	reward_table.75FE7CDF68581EDE.title: "铁路工艺:随机&7[RailCraft: Random]&f"
	reward_table.79C7738D7CEDABD4.title: "神秘农业:第5级 &a种子袋&f&7[MA: Tier 5 Seed Bag]&f"
	reward_table.7FB97C5850827C71.title: "气动工艺:高级等级&7[PNC: Advanced Tier]&f"
	quest.0B19BF090C21FDB9.quest_desc: ["在空岛世界中,寻找动物可能很麻烦.&a农贸市场&f旨在让这变得更容易,让你可以用一颗钻石的价格购买某些动物的&a刷怪蛋&f.我甚至会免费送你一颗钻石.\\n&7[In a Skyblock world, it can be troublesome to find animals. The Market aims to make that easier, by letting you purchase Spawn Eggs of certain animals, at the cost of a Diamond. I'll even give you a Diamond on the house.]&f"]
	quest.0B19BF090C21FDB9.quest_subtitle: "动物&a刷怪蛋&f&7[Animal Spawn Eggs]&f"
	quest.0D6D45DBA64E612D.quest_desc: ["最大生成延迟是刷怪笼生成生物可能需要的最长时间.就像最小延迟一样,它可以低至20,高至32,767.每个时钟会将刷怪笼的速度修改10.速度以游戏刻表示,其中20游戏刻等于&a1秒&f.所以最快的生成延迟将是每次生成之间间隔&a1秒&f.\\n&7[The Maximum Spawn Delay is how long it could take to spawn mobs. Just like the Minimum it can be as low as 20 to as high as 32,767. Each Clock modifies the speed of the spawner by 10. The speed is expressed in ticks where 20 ticks equals 1 second. So quickest spawn delay would be 1 second between each.]&f"]
	quest.0D6D45DBA64E612D.title: "最大生成延迟&7[Maximum Spawn Delay]&f"
	quest.0E02CE4469FCA4C9.quest_desc: ["红石激活为你的刷怪笼提供了一个开关.没有红石信号时,它将不会生成生物.\\n&7[Redstone Activation gives your spawner an on/off switch. Without Redstone Power it will not spawn.]&f"]
	quest.0E02CE4469FCA4C9.title: "红石激活&7[Redstone Active]&f"
	quest.0F0E227FC3EC0D90.quest_desc: ["这些是除&d神化刷怪笼&f外其他模组提供的刷怪笼.\\n&7[These are spawners provided by mods besides Apothic Spawners.]&f"]
	quest.0F89BFD4A3F63A48.quest_desc: ["一些生物(主要是怪物)需要特定的光照等级才能生成.敌对生物需要较低的光照等级,而被动生物需要较高的光照等级.使用&a灵魂灯笼&f可以让你永远不用担心光照等级,因为它会忽略光照!但这不会忽略其他生成要求,比如牲畜动物需要草方块.\\n&7[Some mobs (mostly monsters) need certain Light Levels to spawn. Hostile ones needing lower levels and passive needing higher ones. Using a Soul Lantern makes it so you never have to worry about Light Levels as it ignores them! This does not ignore other requirements for spawning like livestock animals needing Grass.]&f"]
	quest.0F89BFD4A3F63A48.title: "忽略光照&7[Ignore Light]&f"
	quest.1102B27CBF564127.quest_desc: ["&a刷怪箱激发器&f与其他列出的修改物品不同,这个物品由&d气动工艺&f提供,而不是&d神化刷怪笼&f.如果整合包中没有&d神化刷怪笼&f模组,在刷怪笼上放置激发器将使刷怪笼无论玩家在哪里都会生成生物.而有了&d神化刷怪笼&f(是的,我们有这个模组),它不会改变这一点,而是会防止生成的生物在你离开区块时消失.\\n&7[Spawner Agitators are different from the other listed Modification items, this one is provided by PneumaticCraft instead of Apothic Spawners. Without the Apothic Spawners mod being in the Modpack, having an Agitator on a Spawner will make it spawn mobs no matter where the Player is. With Apothic Spawners, which yes we do have, it won't change that but rather will keep spawned mobs from despawning incase you leave the chunks.]&f"]
	quest.1102B27CBF564127.quest_subtitle: "别在我面前消失,怪物们&7[Don't you despawn on me, Mobs]&f"
	quest.167E1474644C9908.quest_desc: ["&a石英&f会使其他物品对刷怪笼产生相反的效果.当你副手持石英,主手持其他&a刷怪箱修改&f物品时,它会执行与其原本作用相反的操作.使用石英和&a烈焰棒&f,不会增加&a生成范围&f,而是会减少它.使用石英和&a恶魂之泪&f,则会减少最大实体数量.\\n&7[The Quartz makes whatever the other item does, it does the opposite for the Spawner. With Quartz in your offhand and the other Spawner Modification item in your main it will do the opposite of its role. With Quartz and Blaze Rods instead of increasing Spawn Range it will decrease it. With Quartz and Ghast Tears it'll decrease Max Entities.]&f"]
	quest.167E1474644C9908.title: "相反日&7[Opposite Day]&f"
	quest.186593EBCE3FE8D8.quest_desc: ["&a生成范围&f是生物可以生成的区域.范围越大,它们生成的空间就越大.范围越小,工厂的成本就越低.\\n&7[The Spawn Range is the area of where mobs can spawn. The bigger the area, the more room for them to spawn in. The smaller the area the cheaper the factory.]&f"]
	quest.186593EBCE3FE8D8.title: "&a生成范围&f&7[Spawn Range]&f"
	quest.18E0F5A78F696FA3.quest_desc: ["回响碎片会给刷怪笼一个特殊效果.任何生成的生物,其掉落的战利品都会倍增.\\n&7[Echo shards give a special effect to the spawner. Any mobs spawned will have the loot that they drop multiplied.]&f"]
	quest.18E0F5A78F696FA3.title: "回响&7[Echoing]&f"
	quest.1AD87CB3226ED224.quest_desc: ["羊毛只对刷怪笼做一件事,那就是让它安静下来.不喜欢听到愚蠢的刷怪笼噪音？那就用羊毛!任何颜色、纱支数或设计都可以!\\n&7[Wool only does one thing to the spawner and that's to shut it up. Don't like hearing the stupid Spawner noises? Then use Wool! Any color, thread count, or design!]&f"]
	quest.1AD87CB3226ED224.title: "安静点,你会吵醒怪物的!&7[Quiet down you'll wake up the mobs!]&f"
	quest.21C2458FED19363C.quest_desc: ["它使用&a精华&r以及&a生物捕捉工具&f中的生物来生成该生物的副本.\\n&7[It uses Essence along with a mob in a Mob Imprisonment Tool to spawn a copy of that mob.]&f"]
	quest.21C2458FED19363C.quest_subtitle: "&d工业先锋&f的刷怪笼&7[Industrial Foregoing's Spawner]&f"
	quest.223A5BDB5056B781.quest_desc: ["捕捉是一个剑的附魔,可以让生物有几率掉落它们的蛋.这是一个稀有附魔,所以继续寻找吧,并查看&5&l&d神化附魔&f&r来获得帮助.每一级都会让你每次击杀有0.5%的几率获得一个蛋,通常你能获得的最高等级是VII(7).\\n&7[Capturing is an Enchantment for Swords to make Mobs rarely drop their Eggs. It's a rare one so keep looking for one and check out lApothic Enchanting to help. Every level gives you a 0.5% chance at getting an Egg each kill and the highest level you can normally get is VII (7).]&f"]
	quest.263860CADB3D76C6.quest_desc: ["&a电动刷怪笼&f是使用&d末影接口&f制作的&a队伍内刷怪蛋&f.首先,你需要一个装满的&a灵魂瓶&f和一个破损的刷怪笼.(技术上你只需要&a灵魂瓶&f来改变刷怪笼的类型,但无所谓了).一旦你有了一个喜欢的破损刷怪笼,用它来合成&a电动刷怪笼&f!然后,放置它,给它一个电容器,并供能.砰!现在你正在用&d末影接口&f生成生物了.\\n\\n你也可以让这个刷怪笼直接填充&a灵魂瓶&f,而无需点击器.\\n&7[Powered Spawner is the Mob Spawner made using EnderIO. First, you'll need a filled Soul Vial and a Broken Spawner. (Technically you only need the Soul Vial to change the Spawner but that's whatever). Once you have a Broken Spawner you like, craft the Powered Spawner with it! Then, place it down, give it a Capacitor, and power it. Boom! now you are spawning mobs with EnderIO.\\n\\nYou can also make this Spawner fill Soul Vials directly, without the need of a Clicker.]&f"]
	quest.263860CADB3D76C6.quest_subtitle: "&d末影接口&f的刷怪笼&7[EnderIO's Spawner]&f"
	quest.2D8A7065F8CDDDDD.quest_desc: ["拭子是我获取&a刷怪蛋&f最喜欢的方式,你需要使用怪物磨碎工具来实现.只需用拭子&a右击&f一个生物,然后用它、种子和一桶任何类型的&a经验流体&r来合成&a鸡饲料&f.我不在乎你为此使用哪种类型的&a经验流体&f.一旦你有了鸡饲料,喂给一只鸡.不幸的是,这只鸡无法在过程中存活,但是,嘿,&a刷怪蛋&f!\\n\\n不过,并非所有生物都可以被拭子取样.\\n&7[Swabs are my favorite way of getting Spawn Eggs, you'll need to use Mob Grinding Utils for it. Simply right click a mob with the Swab then craft Chicken Feed with it, seeds, and a bucket of any kind of XP Fluid. I don't care which type of XP Fluid you use for this. Once you have that, feed a Chicken it. Unfortunately the Chicken won't survive the procedure but hey, Spawn Eggs!\\n\\nNot all mobs can be swabbed, though.]&f"]
	quest.2FE4B7B70D90A455.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6ATM团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于ATM整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6ATM&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下,未经&6ATM团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6ATM团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.30EB438C66324213.quest_desc: ["&a下界之星&f会做海晶碎片所做的事,但效果更好.玩家不再需要靠近刷怪笼.只要其所在区块被加载,它就会生成生物.\\n&7[A Nether Star will do what the Prismarine Shards do but much better. Players no longer need to be near the spawner. As long as its chunk-loaded it will spawn.]&f"]
	quest.30EB438C66324213.title: "忽略玩家&7[Ignore Players]&f"
	quest.310969B8FE0A94DE.quest_desc: ["&d神化&f带来的另一个游戏改变是刷怪笼.还记得能用&a精准采集&f挖掘刷怪笼吗？多亏了&d神化&f,它回来了!你还可以通过&a右击&f以下任何物品来为刷怪笼添加许多新的修改.\\n&7[Another game change Apotheosis brings is to Spawners. Remember being able to mine Spawners with Silk Touch? Well it's back thanks to Apotheosis! There's also many new Modifications you can add to Spawners by right clicking any of these items.]&f"]
	quest.310969B8FE0A94DE.title: "&d神化刷怪笼&f&7[Apothic Spawners]&f"
	quest.39E822440E7D2E04.quest_desc: ["Mob Grinding Utils 的核心就是 &a怪物农场&f,所以它当然有一个生成器!那就是 &a实体生成器&f!不过它需要三样东西才能工作:一个 &a刷怪蛋&f、经验果冻宝宝和一个红石信号.经验果冻宝宝是通过将经验值在 &a经验固化器&f 中用 &a经验果冻宝宝模具&f 加工而成.它们 &a可食用&f 或用作第二个槽位中的燃料.一旦你在顶部槽位放入 &a刷怪蛋&f,第二个槽位放入经验果冻宝宝,并提供一个红石信号,它就会开始生成怪物了!\\n&7[Mob Grinding Utils is all about Mob Farming so of course it has a Spawner! The Entity Spawner! It'll need 3 things to work though: a Spawn Egg, XP Jelly Babies, and a Redstone signal. XP Jelly Babies are made by processing XP through a XP Solidifier with the XP Mould Jelly Baby. They can be eaten or used as Fuel in the second slot. Once you have the Spawn Egg in the top slot, XP Jelly Babies in the Second, and a Redstone signal it'll start spawning the mobs!]&f"]
	quest.39E822440E7D2E04.quest_subtitle: "Mob Grinding Utils 的刷怪笼&7[Mob Grinding Utils' Spawner]&f"
	quest.3E2A411FF5B4B0E7.quest_desc: ["&a激活范围&f 是指玩家(你)必须距离生成器多近它才会工作.最小距离可以是 1 格,最大是 48 格半径.\\n&7[Activation Range is how close the Player (You) must be to the Spawner for it to work. The lowest it can be is 1 block away and the highest is a 48 block radius.]&f"]
	quest.3E2A411FF5B4B0E7.title: "&a激活范围&f&7[Activation Range]&f"
	quest.3F55F3CC8519D783.quest_desc: ["&a灵魂&f刷怪笼是&d神秘农业&f赠予我们的刷怪笼.它使用怪物精华和能量来生成怪物.怪物精华通过收获怪物植物获得,而怪物植物由&a灵魂瓶&f制成.所以你得先杀死怪物,或者使用&a灵魂提取器&f.\\n&7[The Soulium Spawner is the Spawner gifted to us by Mystical Agriculture. It uses Mob Essence and Energy to spawn the mobs. Mob Essence is gotten through harvesting Mob Plants, made by Soul Jars. So you'll have to kill the mobs first, or use the Soul Extractor.]&f"]
	quest.3F55F3CC8519D783.quest_subtitle: "&d神秘农业&f的刷怪笼&7[Mystical Agriculture's Spawner]&f"
	quest.40096ED0B04C3EC5.quest_desc: ["所有刷怪笼的必需品.当它说忽略所有条件时,指的是大部分条件.它会忽略光照等级、生成所需的方块以及生物群系.不过,空间条件仍然需要满足,比如史莱姆需要3x3的区域才能生成,玩家也需要在附近.\\n&7[The must-need for all Spawners. When it says ignores all conditions, it means most. Ignores light levels, blocks needing for spawning, and biomes. Space conditions are still needed though, like slimes needing 3x3 area to spawn, and same goes with players needing to be nearby.]&f"]
	quest.40096ED0B04C3EC5.title: "忽略所有条件&7[Ignore All Conditions]&f"
	quest.42D7C8CD8E6F5CD7.quest_desc: ["在刷怪笼上使用&a紫颂果果实&f,你将吸走即将生成的怪物的灵魂,只留下它们曾经的空壳.怪物将失去所有AI,因此它们基本上会像盔甲架一样.它们无法攻击你,无法传送,无法自主移动.它们就待在那里等着被杀死,多么令人兴奋!\\n&7[By using a Chorus Fruit on a Spawner you suck the souls out the mobs that will be spawned, only leaving a hollow husk of what they used to be. The mobs will lose all AI so they will do basically what an armor stand does. They can't hit you, can't teleport, can't move on their own. They sit there ready to be killed, how exciting!]&f"]
	quest.42D7C8CD8E6F5CD7.title: "无AI&7[No AI]&f"
	quest.4D07B0A4A2E77CDA.quest_desc: ["最大实体数量是指一个刷怪笼可以生成并保留的怪物数量.如果最大实体数仅为6,那么当已有6个怪物时,除非它们死亡或离开,否则不会再生成更多.每个&a恶魂之泪&f会使该数量增加或减少2个实体.最大为16个实体,最小为1个.\\n&7[Max entities is the amount of mobs that can be spawned by a spawner and kept. If it's only 6 max entities when 6 mobs are already spawned no more will spawned until they're dead or moved. Each Ghast Tear brings it up or down 2 Entities. Max of 16 Entities and Minimum of 1.]&f"]
	quest.4D07B0A4A2E77CDA.title: "最大实体数量&7[Max Entities]&f"
	quest.4F7F8F4ED1CA0550.quest_desc: ["在刷怪笼上使用营火会使生成的怪物着火.非常适合制作美味的牛排.\\n&7[A Campfire used on the spawner will have the mobs spawn on fire. Perfect for a nice Steak.]&f"]
	quest.4F7F8F4ED1CA0550.title: "燃烧&7[Burning]&f"
	quest.52FAF122466FDDC9.quest_desc: ["稳定刷怪笼是&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f版本的刷怪笼.当你在一个刷怪笼上使用核心时,它会变成一个稳定刷怪笼.你可以更换核心,但无法更改属性,因为现在它们由核心决定.核心越好,生成的怪物越多,速度也越快.\\n&7[Stabilized Spawner is Draconic Evolution's version of the Spawner. When you use one of the Cores on a Spawner it will become a Stabilized Spawner. You can swap the Cores but you won't be able to change the stats as now they are set by the Cores. The better the Core the more mobs spawn and at a faster rate.]&f"]
	quest.52FAF122466FDDC9.quest_subtitle: "&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f's Spawner&7[Draconic Evolution's Spawner]&f"
	quest.6A497B063CF32A5C.quest_desc: ["发酵蛛眼可用于增加刷怪笼可能生成的怪物数量.生成的怪物数量是随机的,最大数量由该数值决定.每个眼睛会使该数量增加或减少1,最大为16.\\n&7[A Fermented Spider's Eye can be used to increase the amount of mobs that CAN spawn from a spawner. The Mobs spawned is random with a Maximum amount determined by the number. It goes up or down by 1 for each eye to a maximum of 16.]&f"]
	quest.6A497B063CF32A5C.title: "&a生成数量&f&7[Spawn Count]&f"
	quest.6D3B958E49AE7BDB.quest_desc: ["护符碎片可以制成护符或&a刷怪蛋&f.它们来自&d圣遗物&f,由相应的怪物稀有掉落.有些甚至可以通过合成获得!取两个碎片和一个普通的鸡蛋,你就可以合成一个&a刷怪蛋&f.\\n&7[Charm Fragments can be made either into Charms or Spawn Eggs. They are from Reliquary and rarely drop from their respective mobs. Some can even be crafted! Take 2 and a normal Egg and you can craft a Spawn Egg.]&f"]
	quest.6D68D9941049E806.quest_desc: ["这个刷怪笼,顾名思义,将利用&d源力&r作为燃料.要决定生成哪种怪物,你需要一个在该区域内关押着怪物的&d禁锢罐&r.\\n&7[This spawner will, as its name implies, make use of Source as fuel. To decide on a mob to spawn, you'll need a Containment Jar holding the mob in the area.]&f"]
	quest.6D68D9941049E806.quest_subtitle: "&d新生魔艺&f的刷怪笼&7[Ars Nouveau's Spawner]&f"
	quest.6F71FD826C29C31A.quest_desc: ["对于从早期版本回归的玩家来说,这个可能比较新.在刷怪笼上使用海龟蛋,它将只生成其中怪物的幼年版本.这只对原版怪物的幼年版本有效,对模组怪物无效.\\n&7[This one might be new to ones returning from earlier versions. By using a turtle egg on a spawner, it will only spawn in baby versions of the mobs in it. This only works with Vanilla baby versions of mobs, not modded.]&f"]
	quest.6F71FD826C29C31A.title: "幼年化&7[Youthful]&f"
	quest.72AE56D34834D28E.quest_desc: ["又一个来自&d气动工艺&f？哦,这个才是真正的刷怪笼,我明白了.和龙之研究的稳定刷怪笼一样,你首先需要一个原版刷怪笼.有了之后,放置一个刷怪笼提取器&a或更高级别&f在刷怪笼上,并给予低于-0.5巴的压力使其工作.完成后,它会给你一个&a刷怪笼核心&f,里面装满了原刷怪笼中的怪物,并留下一个&a空刷怪笼&f.然后用&a空刷怪笼&f合成一个&a气动刷怪笼&f,再将&a刷怪笼核心&f放入其中.(要升级核心,使用&a真空陷阱&f吸入怪物,它们会进入&a刷怪笼核心&f).完成后,刷怪笼现在需要压力才能工作,忽略光照等级,并由红石信号激活.\\n&7[Another one from PneumaticCraft? Oh this one is the actual Spawner I see. Like the Draconic Stabilized Spawner you'll need a Vanilla Spawner first. Once you have one, place a Spawner Extrator above the Spawner and give it below -0.5 Bars to get it to work. Once it's done it'll give you a Spawner Core filled with whatever mob was in it and it will leave you with an Empty Spawner. Then use the Empty Spawner to craft a Pressurized Spawner and then put the Spawner Core into it. (To upgrade the Core use a Vacuum Trap to suck up the mobs that will go into the Spawner Core). Once you do that the Spawner will now need Pressure to work, ignores Light Level, and is Redstone Activated.]&f"]
	quest.72AE56D34834D28E.quest_subtitle: "&d气动工艺&f的刷怪笼&7[PneumaticCraft's Spawner]&f"
	quest.77A8E8122870BBCE.quest_desc: ["这严格来说不是一个&a刷怪蛋&f,但由于它能将怪物绑定到刷怪笼上,我还是把它放在这里.查看&5&l&d神化附魔&f&r章节以了解更多关于如何获得这根&d神化之缚&r的信息.\\n&7[This is technically not a Spawn Egg, but I'm including it here anyway, due to its ability to bind mobs to Spawners. Check out the lApothic Enchanting chapter to learn more about how to get this Lead.]&f"]
	quest.77A8E8122870BBCE.quest_subtitle: "那不是&a刷怪蛋&f!&7[That's no Spawn Egg!]&f"
	quest.78E94C386B1E7359.quest_desc: ["通常你无法获得&a刷怪蛋&f,但刷怪笼也是如此,而我们就在这里!有几种方法可以获得&a刷怪蛋&f,一旦获得,在刷怪笼上&a右击&f它来改变其生成的怪物.\\n&7[Usually you can't get Spawn Eggs, but that's the same with Spawners and here we are! There's a few ways of obtaining Spawn Eggs but once you do, right click it on a Spawner to change the mobs it spawns.]&f"]
	quest.7A9AE63998BB41FF.quest_desc: ["为了决定何时生成,刷怪笼会在最大和最小生成延迟之间随机选择一个数字.最小延迟可以低至20,高至32,767.每块糖会使最小延迟增加或减少10.\\n&7[To determine when the Spawner will spawn it picks a random number between maximum and minimum spawn delay. The Minimum can be as low as 20 to as high as 32,767. Each piece of sugar modifies the min delay up or down by 10.]&f"]
	quest.7A9AE63998BB41FF.title: "最小生成延迟&7[Minimum Spawn Delay]&f"
	quest.7F6B66566C211735.quest_desc: ["在刷怪笼上使用滴水石锥会降低生成怪物的最大生命值.这可以将它们的生命值降低至最低20%.\\n&7[Dripstone used on the spawner will reduce the max health of the mob spawned. This can decrease their health to as low as 20%]&f"]
	quest.7F6B66566C211735.title: "生命值&7[Health]&f"
	task.24893D6EDE0BD819.title: "&a怪物护符&f碎片&7[Mob Charm Fragments]&f"
	task.39702880D9133E3E.title: "羊毛&7[Wool]&f"
	task.3B219688DA1CF9C8.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.45250DA4433007C6.title: "捕获之书&7[Capturing Books]&f"
	task.524CBF7058496E7F.title: "其他刷怪笼&7[Other Spawners]&f"
	task.55587BA32D30318C.title: "&a刷怪蛋&f&7[Spawn Eggs]&f"
	task.73B56F2139A98F77.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.001C1881E9289566.quest_desc: ["&9稀有&r是稀有度的中间等级.\\n\\n它出现在所有&l世界阶层&r中,但在&l世界阶层:&e攀升&r中最常见.\\n\\n&9&a发光水晶碎片&f&r是通过在&c&l回收台&r中使用&9稀有&r&e物品&r制成的.\\n&7[Rare is the middle ground of Rarities. \\n\\nIt appears in all lWorld Tiers but most common in lWorld Tier: Ascent. \\n\\nLuminous Crystal Shards are made from using Rare Items in a lSalvaging Table.]&f"]
	quest.001C1881E9289566.quest_subtitle: "&9稀有&7[Rare]&f"
	quest.001C1881E9289566.title: "&9&a发光水晶碎片&f&7[Luminous Crystal Shard]&f"
	quest.0089A394566B0F3B.quest_desc: ["&a罕见&r是第二级稀有度.\\n\\n它开始出现在&l世界阶层:&9避风港&r,在&l世界阶层:&2边疆&r最为丰富,并在&l世界阶层:&4巅峰&r停止出现.\\n\\n&a时光织物&r是通过在&c&l回收台&r中使用&a罕见&r&e物品&r制成的.\\n&7[Uncommon is the second Rarity. \\n\\nIt starts appearing in lWorld Tier: Haven, most abundant in lWorld Tier: Frontier, and stops in lWorld Tier: Pinnacle. \\n\\nTimeworn Fabric is made from using Uncommon Items in a lSalvaging Table.]&f"]
	quest.0089A394566B0F3B.quest_subtitle: "&a罕见&7[Uncommon]&f"
	quest.0089A394566B0F3B.title: "&a时光织物&7[Timeworn Fabric]&f"
	quest.097FDC136BC843A7.quest_desc: ["&l世界阶层:&6顶峰&r需要你将&e盔甲&r和&e工具/武器&r从&a罕见&r升级到&9稀有&r(或更好)!你还需要杀死&0&l&a凋灵&f&r.\\n\\n&0&l&a凋灵&f&r不必是&4入侵者&r,说实话,如果不是会更简单.\\n\\n在&6&l顶峰&r,&5史诗&r&e物品&f和&2宝石&r将是最常见的,对于&e物品&r,你现在可以获得&6神话&r,而对于&a宝石&r,你可以找到&z完美&r.同样,两者都极其稀有!\\n\\n现在我们将获得75%的经验获取和50%的幸运值.\\n\\n&4怪物&r也将被强化,获得12点&a护甲值&f、10点&a盔甲韧性&f、15点护甲穿透和10点保护穿透.\\n\\n是我的错觉吗,还是它们的升级比我们的更好？\\n&7[lWorld Tier: Summit will need you to upgrade your Armor and Tool/Weapon from Uncommon to Rare (or better)! You'll also need to kill lThe Wither. \\n\\nlThe Wither doesn't need to be an Invader and honestly, it'll be easier if he isn't. \\n\\nIn lSummit Epic Items and Gems will be the most common, and for Items you can now get Mythic and with Gems you can find zPerfect. Again, both being extremely rare! \\n\\nNow we'll get 75% Experience Gained and 50% Luck. \\n\\nMonsters will also be buffed to get 12 Armor Points, 10 Armor Toughness, 15 Armor Pierce, and 10 Protection Pierce. \\n\\nIs it just me or are their upgrades better than ours?]&f"]
	quest.097FDC136BC843A7.title: "&l世界阶层:&6顶峰&7[lWorld Tier: Summit]&f"
	quest.099C2A9B9CA138F8.quest_desc: ["&6神话&r是我们能获得的最强大的物品之一!\\n\\n&6神话&r物品仅在&l世界阶层:&6顶峰&r和&l世界阶层:&4巅峰&r中找到,在后者中最为常见.\\n\\n&6神铸珍珠&r是通过在&c&l回收台&r中使用&6神话&r&e物品&r制成的.\\n&7[Mythic are some of the greatest we can get! \\n\\nMythics are found only in lWorld Tier: Summit and in lWorld Tier: Pinnacle, where they are most common. \\n\\nGodforged Pearls are made from using Mythic Items in a lSalvaging Table.]&f"]
	quest.099C2A9B9CA138F8.quest_subtitle: "&6神话&7[Mythic]&f"
	quest.099C2A9B9CA138F8.title: "&6神铸珍珠&7[Godforged Pearl]&f"
	quest.1403D677CF2815C3.quest_desc: ["&5&l重铸台&r能做&9&l简易&r重铸台所做的一切,而且更好!\\n\\n它可以为我们提供&5史诗&r和&6神话&r&e词缀&r,以及我们之前已有的词缀!\\n&7[The lReforging Table does everything the lSimple one will do, but better! \\n\\nIt can give us Epic and Mythic Affixes along with our previous ones!]&f"]
	quest.1403D677CF2815C3.title: "(更好的)&5&l重铸台&r&7[(Better) lReforging Table]&f"
	quest.166CE4243896A0CD.quest_desc: ["不喜欢你的&a宝石&r？那就改变它们!\\n\\n要改变你的&a宝石&r的稀有度,你需要使用这个&a&l宝石升级台&r.\\n\\n使用2个相同的&a宝石&r和对应稀有度的材料,你可以提升你的&a宝石&r的稀有度,从而增强其力量.\\n&7[Don't like your Gems? Then, change them! \\n\\nTo change the Rarity of your Gem you'll need to use this lTable. \\n\\nBy using 2 of the same Gem and Rarity Materials, you can increase your Gems Rarity and that increases its power.]&f"]
	quest.166CE4243896A0CD.title: "获得更好的&a宝石&7[Getting better Gems]&f"
	quest.16C74B5F99AD6724.quest_desc: ["&8普通&r是最基础的稀有度.这使得它在游戏早期最常见,但也最弱.\\n\\n&8普通&r在&l世界阶层:&9避风港&r出现最多,并在&l世界阶层:&6顶峰&r之后停止出现.\\n\\n&8神秘的&a废金属&f&r是通过在&c&l回收台&r中使用&8普通&r&e物品&r制成的.\\n&7[Common is the most basic Rarity. This makes it most common to find early game, but also the weakest. \\n\\nCommon shows up most at the lWorld Tier: Haven, and will stop appearing after lWorld Tier: Summit. \\n\\nMysterious Scrap Metals are made from using Common Items in a lSalvaging Table.]&f"]
	quest.16C74B5F99AD6724.quest_subtitle: "&8普通&7[Common]&f"
	quest.16C74B5F99AD6724.title: "&8神秘的&a废金属&f&7[Mysterious Scrap Metals]&f"
	quest.196312DF0D2E2CB6.quest_desc: ["Invaders are what we know as lApotheosis Bosses. \\n\\nThese are Mobs that can spawn in any Dimension and they will always be buffed and have Affixed Items equipped. \\n\\nMost will have more Hearts, Damage, and Effects than normal Mobs! When Killed they'll drop Affixed Items and Gems. \\n\\nThey have their own Rarities align with lApotheosis Rarities. Their Rarities determine what they spawn with and their stats. \\n\\nTheir Rarities are determined by the lWorld Tier! lWorld Tiers are new additions to lApotheosis, they will change the Rarity of Loot and Bosses you can find. \\n\\nTo access the lWorld Tier Menu, Hold CTRL and press T."]
	quest.196312DF0D2E2CB6.title: "&4入侵者/首领&r和&l世界阶层&7[Invaders/Bosses and lWorld Tiers]&f"
	quest.1CD05CB4A3DB112A.quest_desc: ["&c&l回收台&r终于可以让你在不使用&7铁砧&r的情况下获得材料和&9宝石粉尘&r.\\n\\n你可以回收带有&e词缀&r的&e工具&f和&e盔甲&f以获得它们的材料.\\n\\n你获得的&a武器材料&f基于物品的稀有度,&8普通&r物品会给出&8普通&r材料.\\n\\n并且,不知为何,还能分解马/狗盔甲.\\n&7[The lSalvaging Table can finally get you Materials and Gem Dust without using Anvils. \\n\\nYou can recycle Tools and Armor with Affixes to get their Materials. \\n\\nThe Materials you get are based on the Rarity of Item, Common Items will give Common Materials. \\n\\nAnd break down Horse/Dog Armor for some reason.]&f"]
	quest.1CD05CB4A3DB112A.title: "&c&l回收台&7[lSalvaging Table]&f"
	quest.1D1FAA2F86695781.quest_desc: ["对于&l&2边疆&r,&e词缀&r的稀有度无关紧要,但现在对于&l&e攀升&r,你需要所有物品都是&a罕见&r或更好.\\n\\n你还需要杀死一个&4入侵者&r,也就是一个&6&l神化&r首领,来升级你的&l世界阶层&r.&4首领&r的稀有度无关紧要!\\n\\n&e词缀&r最高只会到&5史诗&r,但现在&9稀有&r比其他的更常见.我们也能获得&6神话&r&a宝石&r……只是需要幸运女神的眷顾!\\n\\n说到幸运,我们的幸运值将增加到30%,经验获取将跃升至55%.\\n\\n作为回报,&4怪物&r现在将拥有8点&a护甲值&f和5点护甲穿透.\\n&7[For lFrontier the Rarity of Affixes didn't matter, but now for lAscent you'll need everything being Uncommon or better. \\n\\nYou'll also need to kill an Invader aka an lApothic Boss, to upgrade your lWorld Tier. The Rarity of Boss doesn't matter! \\n\\nAffixes will only stay up to Epic but now Rare is more common than the rest. We can also get Mythic Gems... just only with Lady Luck's Favor! \\n\\nSpeaking of Luck, our Luck will increase to 30% and Experience will jump to 55%. \\n\\nMonsters in return will now have 8 Armor Points and 5 Armor Pierce.]&f"]
	quest.1D1FAA2F86695781.title: "&l世界阶层:&e攀升&7[lWorld Tier: Ascent]&f"
	quest.2002C7EB13626AE7.quest_desc: ["&6&l强化台&r需要不同的燃料才能工作,这种燃料是&6强化符石&r.\\n\\n每次重铸将消耗1个&6强化符石&r,而每次升级将消耗2个!\\n\\n你需要4个&6神铸珍珠&r来制作它们.\\n&7[The lAugmenting Table needs different Fuel to work, and that Fuel is Sigils of Enhancement. \\n\\nEach Reroll will cost 1 Sigil of Enhancement while each Upgrade will cost 2! \\n\\nYou'll need a Godforged Pearl for 4 of them.]&f"]
	quest.2002C7EB13626AE7.title: "&6强化符石&7[Sigil of Enhancement]&f"
	quest.22E57BF23B9BA2C5.quest_desc: ["&6&l&d神化&f&r现已与&a传送门&r整合.\\n\\n有基于每个&l世界阶层&r(除了&l&9避风港&r)的&a传送门&r,提供一波波的怪物和&4入侵者&r.这些&a传送门&r可能只能在它们各自对应的&l世界阶层&r中使用.一旦你击败了最后一波,你会获得各种奖励,有助于完成相应的&l世界阶层&r.\\n\\n与其他&a传送门&r不同,你总共有3条命可用.\\n&7[lApotheosis is now integrated with Gateways.\\n\\nThere are Gateways based on each lWorld Tier (except lHaven), providing waves of monsters and Invaders. These Gateways may only be used within their respective lWorld Tier. Once you beat the final wave, you get a variety of rewards, useful for finishing their respective lWorld Tier.\\n\\nUnlike other Gateways, you have a total of 3 lives to work with.]&f"]
	quest.24D11ED5F4EEDC48.quest_desc: ["对于&6&l&d神化&f&r的新手来说,&9插槽&r可能令人困惑和恼火.\\n\\n简而言之,你的武器和盔甲需要&9插槽&r来使用&a宝石&r.\\n\\n但如果它没有&9插槽&r怎么办？\\n\\n那么你将需要一个&9镶嵌符石&r!\\n\\n在&8&l&a锻造台&f&r中结合你的物品和&9符石&r,然后砰的一声,你最多可以获得2个&9插槽&r.\\n&7[To those new to lApotheosis, Sockets can be confusing and irritating. \\n\\nIn short, your Weapons and Armor need Sockets to use Gems with it. \\n\\nBut what if it doesn't have a Socket? \\n\\nThen you'll need a Sigil of Socketing! \\n\\nCombine your item and Sigil in a lSmithing Table and boom you can get up to 2 Sockets.]&f"]
	quest.24D11ED5F4EEDC48.title: "&9镶嵌符石&7[Sigil of Socketing]&f"
	quest.29EA8E178F8F8FDB.quest_desc: ["&9&l简易重铸台&r 的使用方式类似于 &5&l&a附魔台&f&r,但使用的是 &e词缀&r!\\n\\n要给任何 &e物品&r 添加一个 &e词缀&r,请将 &e物品&r 放在中心槽位.然后,将你的稀有度材料放入 &a左侧&f 槽位.\\n\\n稀有度材料将决定你的 &e物品&r 上获得什么稀有度的 &e词缀&r.这可以用来升级一些物品,例如从 &8普通&r 升级到 &a罕见&r.\\n\\n你将获得 3 个 &e词缀&r 选项供你选择,同样类似于 &5&l&a附魔台&f&r,第二个和第三个选项会更昂贵.\\n\\n使用 &9&l简易重铸台&r,我们最多只能获得 &9稀有&r 级别的 &e词缀&r.\\n&7[The lSimple Reforging Table is used like an lEnchantment Table but with Affixes! \\n\\nTo add an Affix to any Item, place the Item in the center Slot. Then, add your Rarity Material to the left Slot. \\n\\nThe Rarity Material will determine what Rarity Affix you get on your Item. This can be used to upgrade some Items, like from Common to Uncommon. \\n\\nYou will get 3 choices of Affixes you can pick, also similar to an lEnchantment Table the second and third get more expensive. \\n\\nWith the lSimple Reforging Table we can only get up to Rare Affixes.]&f"]
	quest.29EA8E178F8F8FDB.title: "&9&l简易重铸台&7[lSimple Reforging Table]&f"
	quest.2A032EC573B5316C.quest_desc: ["要获得 &l世界层级:&2边疆&r,你显然需要完成 &9&l天堂&r,还需要一些 &e带词缀的物品&r!\\n\\n需要多少？你需要一整套 &e带词缀的盔甲&r 加上一件 &e带词缀的工具&r 或 &e武器&r.\\n\\n现在 &a罕见&r 级别的 &4入侵者&r 和 &a宝石&r 最为丰富,其余按顺序是:&8普通&r、&9稀有&r,还有 &5史诗&r.\\n\\n拥有 &l世界层级:&2边疆&r 的 &a玩家&f 将获得 35% 的 &a经验增益&f 外加 20% 的幸运值!\\n\\n不过,嘿,并非所有事情都会那么容易,现在 &4怪物&r 将额外获得 4 点 &a护甲值&f.\\n&7[To get the lWorld Tier: Frontier, you'll obviously need lHaven done, but also need a few Affixed Items! \\n\\nHow many? You need a full set of Affixed Armor plus an Affixed Tool or Weapon. \\n\\nNow Uncommon Invaders and Gems are most abundant, with the rest following in order: Common, Rare, and also Epic. \\n\\nThe Player with lWorld Tier: Frontier will get a 35% Experience Boost plus 20% Luck! \\n\\nHey, not everything will be easy though, now Monsters will gain 4 Armor Points extra.]&f"]
	quest.2A032EC573B5316C.title: "&l世界层级:&2边疆&r&7[lWorld Tier: Frontier]&f"
	quest.2E5E129F25707C5D.quest_desc: ["&6至尊符记&r!\\n\\n另一个无法合成的符记,与&c恶意&r类似.和&c恶意&r一样,它能强化词缀.但与&c恶意&r不同的是,它会对装备上的&l每一个&r词缀生效,并且在此过程中不会牺牲任何词缀.\\n\\n你可以通过击败&z无尽天启入侵者传送门&r的100波来获得它.\\n&7[The Sigil of Supremacy!\\n\\nAnother sigil that cannot be crafted, similarly to Malice. Like Malice, it can make affixes stronger. Unlike Malice, it does this to EVERY affix on the gear, and will not sacrifice any in the process.\\n\\nYou can obtain this by beating 100 waves of the zEndless Gateway of Apothic Invaders. ]&f"]
	quest.2E5E129F25707C5D.quest_subtitle: "我给无筛网玩法一点甜头&7[I'm throwing Sieveless runs a bone]&f"
	quest.377A41499D8218C9.quest_desc: [
		"第一个&l世界阶层&r是&l&9避风港&r!作为第一个,它是最容易探索和获得的.\\n\\n要获得它,你只需要手持一件&e词缀物品&r!解锁后它会自动设置.\\n\\n&l世界阶层:&9避风港&r有最高的几率获得&8普通&r&a装备&r&f和&a宝石&r.它也可能出现&a罕见&r和极少数&9稀有&r.\\n&7[The 1st lWorld Tier is lHaven! It being the first makes it the easiest to explore with and easiest to obtain. \\n\\nTo get it you just need to hold an Affixed Item in your Hand! It will automatically be set when unlocked. \\n\\nThe lWorld Tier: Haven has highest chances for Common Gear and Gems. It can also have Uncommon and very rarely, Rare.]&f"
		""
		"这也是唯一一个无法与&4入侵者&r战斗的&l世界阶层&r.\\n&7[This is also the only lWorld Tier where Invaders cannot be fought.]&f"
	]
	quest.377A41499D8218C9.title: "&l世界阶层:&9避风港&7[lWorld Tier: Haven]&f"
	quest.38956DC28E317DEF.quest_desc: ["&d重生符记&r是所有&l&9重铸台&r的燃料.\\n\\n它们当然还需要其他材料,以及要改变的目标物品才能工作……\\n\\n至少它们相对容易合成!\\n&7[The Sigil of Rebirth is Fuel for all the lReforging Tables. \\n\\nThey still need the other Material, and obviously the Item it'll change to work though... \\n\\nAtleast they're relatively easier to Craft!]&f"]
	quest.38956DC28E317DEF.title: "&d重生符记&7[Sigil of Rebirth]&f"
	quest.3BF5B8DE7A1CC4D7.quest_desc: ["如果你想要好装备,你将需要&6&l&d神化&f装备&r,而这都始于一颗&a宝石&r!\\n\\n&a宝石&r是稀有&a掉落自&f任何生物的,它们也确认&a掉落自&f&4入侵者&r.\\n\\n你稍后会了解更多关于它们的信息,现在先去刷怪吧!\\n&7[If you want good gear you're gonna need lApotheosis Gear, and that all starts with a Gem! \\n\\nGems are rare Drops from any Mob, they are also confirmed Drops from Invaders. \\n\\nYou'll learn more about those later, for now Farm those Mobs!]&f"]
	quest.3BF5B8DE7A1CC4D7.title: "&6&l&d神化&f冒险&7[lApotheosis Adventure]&f"
	quest.45647395169978ED.quest_desc: ["要获得&9宝石粉&r,你需要一颗&6&l&d神化&f&r&a宝石&r和一个&7&l铁砧&r.\\n\\n任何&6&l&d神化&f&r&a宝石&r都可以(建议只用&8普通&f和&a罕见&r)!\\n\\n一旦你获得了&a宝石&r,就用一个下落的&7&l铁砧&r砸碎它们!\\n\\n然后,你就可以用你的&9宝石粉&r合成一个&c&l回收台&r.\\n&7[To get Gem Dust you need an lApotheosis Gem and an lAnvil. \\n\\nAny lApotheosis Gem (Recommended only Common and Uncommon)! \\n\\nOnce you get your Gems, smash them with a falling lAnvil! \\n\\nThen, you can use your Gem Dust to Craft a lSalvaging Table.]&f"]
	quest.45647395169978ED.title: "&9宝石粉&7[Gem Dust]&f"
	quest.4E9DDDBD8263D0E3.quest_desc: ["&7无名符记&r如其名所示,当你有一件名字长得尴尬的&e词缀物品&r时,你可以在&8&l&a锻造台&f&r中将其与&7符记&r结合,以去除大部分名字.\\n\\n(只有材料、物品类型以及稀有度颜色会保留).\\n&7[Sigil of Unnaming does as the name suggests, when you have an Affixed Item with an awkwardly long name, you can combine it with the Sigil in a lSmithing Table to get rid of most of the name. \\n\\n(Only the Material and Item Type as with the Rarity color will stay).]&f"]
	quest.4E9DDDBD8263D0E3.title: "&7无名符记&7[Sigil of Unnaming]&f"
	quest.552BA5E6FA987256.quest_desc: ["&c恶意符记&r是一个神秘的符记.没人知道如何合成它.有传言说它由&4入侵者&r掉落.\\n\\n它的作用是另一个谜,不过一些玩家发现,他们用在其上的装备会失去一个词缀,同时使另一个不同的词缀变强.被选择进行此操作的词缀,就像符记本身一样,是另一个谜.\\n&7[The Sigil of Malice is a mysterious sigil. No one knows how to craft it. Rumors circulate about it being dropped by Invaders.\\n\\nWhat it does is another mystery, though some players found that they lost an affix from gear they used it on, making a different affix stronger. The affixes chosen for this are, much like the sigil itself, yet another mystery.]&f"]
	quest.57BB2CC6D9D2AE87.quest_desc: ["这才是你真正需要的,用于打造完美&e词缀&r的东西.\\n\\n首先你需要&6&l强化台&r、一件工具和&6强化符记&r.\\n\\n一旦你拥有了所有这些,世界就是你的了!你可以重铸&e词缀&r,选择特定的&e词缀&r,或者升级指定的&e词缀&r!\\n&7[This is what you really need for perfect Affixes. \\n\\nFirst you need the lTable, a Tool, and Sigils of Enhancement. \\n\\nOnce you have all those, the world is all yours! You can reroll Affixes, choose a specific Affix, or upgrade set Affixes!]&f"]
	quest.57BB2CC6D9D2AE87.title: "&6&l强化台&7[lAugmenting Table]&f"
	quest.6667638252DB9C74.quest_desc: ["&8符记&r是用于改变你的&6&l&d神化&f&r&e词缀物品&r的物品；无论是清空&9插槽&r、添加更多&9插槽&r,还是移除名称!\\n\\n所有符记都与你的物品一起在&8&l&a锻造台&f&r、&9&l重铸台&r或&6&l强化台&r中使用.\\n&7[Sigils are items used to change your lApotheosis Affixed Items; whether it be clearing Sockets, adding more Sockets, or removing the Name! \\n\\nAll are used with your Item in a lSmithing Table, lReforging Table, or lAugementing Table.]&f"]
	quest.6667638252DB9C74.quest_subtitle: "现在只讲符记!&7[Just Sigils now!]&f"
	quest.6667638252DB9C74.title: "&m药水和&r&8符记&7[Vials and Sigils]&f"
	quest.6B5B01C612951BAF.quest_desc: ["与其他传送门珍珠不同,这个是通过通关&4&l巅峰&r传送门获得的.\\n\\n不过,这需要以牺牲&z永恒者克雷格&r为代价,这是一个拥有&l大量&r生命值的生物.\\n\\n这个传送门会召唤出无穷无尽、强度逐渐提升的波次,每波之间的间隔时间越来越短.它可以生成来自&l任何&r维度的&4入侵者&r,而不仅仅是你使用它的那个维度.这也意味着你可以获得通常仅限于其他维度的宝石,例如末地之外的末影涌动宝石.\\n\\n如果你能击败100波,你就可以获得……\\n&7[Unlike other Gate Pearls, this one is obtained by clearing the lPinnacle Gateway.\\n\\nIt will come with the sacrifice of zCraig the 位阶l, a creature with a LOT of health, though.\\n\\nThis gateway will summon an endless stream of increasingly scaling waves, with less and less time between each one. It can spawn Invaders from ANY dimension, not just the dimension you used it in. This also means you can get gems normally exclusive to other dimensions, such as Endersurge Gems outside of The End.\\n\\nIf you can beat 100 waves, you can get...]&f"]
	quest.6B5B01C612951BAF.title: "&z传送门珍珠 - 无尽天启入侵者传送门&7[zGate Pearl - Endless Gateway of Apothic Invaders]&f"
	quest.6EF206A0BD5BAC0A.quest_desc: ["&5史诗&r终于开始迈向更强大的行列.\\n\\n&5史诗&r在&l世界阶层:&2边疆&r之后出现,并且在&l世界阶层:&4巅峰&r中最常见.\\n\\n&5玄奥沙&r是通过在&c&l回收台&r中使用&5史诗&r&e物品&r制成的.\\n&7[Epic is finally climbing more to the overpowered side. \\n\\nEpic appears after lWorld Tier: Frontier and is most common in lWorld Tier: Pinnacle. \\n\\nArcane Sands are made from using Epic Items in a lSalvaging Table.]&f"]
	quest.6EF206A0BD5BAC0A.quest_subtitle: "&5史诗&7[Epic]&f"
	quest.6EF206A0BD5BAC0A.title: "&5玄奥沙&7[Arcane Sands]&f"
	quest.7080F026A37F1832.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods 团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r为用于 AllTheMods 整合包而创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下授权,未经&6AllTheMods 团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods 团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.7C90008081DEBECA.quest_desc: ["你有了&e工具&r,也有了&a宝石&r……那么我们如何组合它们？\\n\\n首先,确保你的&e工具&r有一个开放的&9插槽&r.(关于&9插槽&r的更多信息,请查看符记部分).\\n\\n如果有一个是开放的,你可以在&8&l&a锻造台&f&r中组合你的&e工具&r和&a宝石&r.\\n\\n如果你对当前的&a宝石&r不满意,那么你可能需要一个不同的工作台!\\n&7[You got Tools and you got Gems... so how do we combine them? \\n\\nFirst, make sure your Tool has an open Socket. (For more on Sockets check the Sigils section). \\n\\nIf one is open, you can combine your Tool and Gem in a lSmithing Table. \\n\\nIf you aren't happy with your current Gems then you might need a different Table!]&f"]
	quest.7C90008081DEBECA.title: "应用&a宝石&r(及其他)&7[Applying Gems (and others)]&f"
	quest.7CB03F92F9ECEFFB.quest_desc: ["值得庆幸的是,&6&l&d神化&f&r使得从&e工具&r中取出&9插槽&r变得容易多了!\\n\\n现在,你不再需要选择是保留&e工具&r还是&a宝石&r,而是可以两者都保留.\\n\\n在&8&l&a锻造台&f&r中使用&a提取符记&r和一件&e词缀工具&r,你就可以将&a宝石&r从中分离出来.\\n&7[Thankfully lApotheosis has made taking Sockets out of Tools much easier! \\n\\nNow instead of having to choose whether to save the Tool or Gem you can now keep both. \\n\\nUse the Sigil of Withdrawal with an Affixed Tool in a lSmithing Table and you'll separate the Gem from it.]&f"]
	quest.7CB03F92F9ECEFFB.title: "&a提取符记&7[Sigil of Withdrawal]&f"
	quest.7EF873DCEB3B9D48.quest_desc: ["最后一个&l世界阶层&r,&l世界阶层:&4巅峰&r.要获得它,你需要至少击杀一次&d&l&a末影龙&f&r,并装备全套&5史诗&r或&6神话&r&e护甲&f和&e工具/武器&r.\\n\\n现在&5史诗&r和&6神话&r对于&a宝石&f和&e工具&r来说是最常见的,而且我们更有可能获得&z完美&r宝石!这以失去&8普通&r和&a罕见&r为代价,但嘿,谁会想念它们呢!\\n\\n按照同样的升级模式,我们将获得125%的经验获取和100%的幸运提升.\\n\\n&4怪物&r将获得它们的最终升级,获得:16&a护甲值&f、20&a盔甲韧性&f、25点护甲穿透和20点保护穿透.\\n&7[The last lWorld Tier, lWorld Tier: Pinnacle. To get it, you'll need to Kill the lEnder Dragon atleast once, and equip all Epic or Mythic Armor and Tool/Weapon. \\n\\nNow Epic and Mythic are most common for Gems and Tools, plus we are more likely to get zPerfect gems! This comes at the loss of Common and Uncommon but hey, who'll miss them! \\n\\nOn the same pattern of upgrades we'll get 125% Experience Gained and 100% Luck increase. \\n\\nMonsters will receive their final upgrade, getting: 16 Armor Points, 20 Armor Toughness, 25 Armor Pierce, and 20 Protection Pierce.]&f"]
	quest.7EF873DCEB3B9D48.title: "&l世界阶层:&4巅峰&7[lWorld Tier: Pinnacle]&f"
	task.1F073FD0F4A296A3.title: "天启传送门&7[Apothic Gateways]&f"
	task.31C72EBA091270E7.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.67D884FA6DD22065.title: "任何&d神化&f宝石&7[Any Apotheosis Gem]&f"
	quest.001A348054127235.quest_desc: ["&5&a紫水晶母岩&f&r可用于合成配方,甚至只是生长&5紫水晶&r!\\n\\n使用一块&5&a紫水晶块&f&r、&a60点永恒&r、介于&c30%&f和&c50%&r之间的&c量子&r,以及&50%奥术&r,我们可以&d&l灌注&r一个.\\n\\n要获得所有这些属性,我们可以使用15个&4发光地狱书架&r和4个&2西瓜书架&r.\\n&7[Budding Amethyst can be useful for Crafting Recipes and even just Growing Amethyst! \\n\\nWith a Amethyst Block, 60 位阶, between 30% and 50% 量子化, and 50% 阿卡那 we can lInfuse one. \\n\\nTo get all those stats we can use 15 Glowing Hellshelves and 4 Melonshelves.]&f"]
	quest.001A348054127235.title: "制作&5&a紫水晶母岩&f&7[Making Budding Amethyst]&f"
	quest.0518551637F76C50.quest_desc: ["对于&9回响&r升级,我们需要一些不同的物品.\\n\\n蜡烛相对容易获得!还有&9&a回响碎片&f&r……这绝对不容易……\\n\\n获得它们的最佳机会是用&c下界合金&r筛网筛一些&e&a压纹末地石&f&r,但你也可以用几种不同的仪式来合成它们.\\n\\n(甚至稍后可以通过&5附魔&r获得!)\\n\\n&9回响深层书架&r将提供更多的&5阿卡那&r,达到&515%&r!同时将最大&a位阶&r提升至&a75&r.\\n&7[For the Echoing upgrade we'll need a few different Items. \\n\\nCandles which are relatively easy to get! And Echo Shards... which definitely aren't... \\n\\nThe best chance at getting them is by sieving some Crushed End Stone with a Netherite Mesh, but you can Craft them with a few different Rituals. \\n\\n(Or even later on with Enchanting!) \\n\\nThe Echoing Deepshelves will give a whole lot more 阿卡那 at 15%! Along with raising the max 位阶 to 75.]&f"]
	quest.0518551637F76C50.title: "&9回响深层书架&7[Echoing Deepshelf]&f"
	quest.0A3C464EF7CDD5F6.quest_desc: [
		"&4地狱书架&r是你接触&c量子&r的入门,它们提供&c3%量子&r和&a3点永恒&r.\\n\\n比普通书架好,对吧？\\n\\n下一步你将需要16个,在&5&a附魔台&f&r周围放置15个&4地狱书架&r,并在你的物品栏中留1个.\\n\\n先制作前11个,我会给你最后的5个&4地狱书架&r!\\n&7[Hellshelves are your introduction to 量子化, they give 3% 量子化 and 3 位阶. \\n\\nBetter than normal Shelves right? \\n\\nYou're going to want 16 of them for the next step, 15 Hellshelves around the Enchantment Table, with 1 in your Inventory. \\n\\nMake the first 11 and I'll give you the last 5 Hellshelves!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/apothic/enchant_hellshelf.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0A3C464EF7CDD5F6.title: "&4地狱书架&7[Hellshelves]&f"
	quest.0F3A0A4DC18E5E55.quest_desc: ["&a位阶&r设定&5附魔等级&r,这决定了你可以或将会获得什么&5附魔&r!\\n\\n它的默认值是&a0&r,最大值是&a100&r.\\n\\n几乎所有的&7书架&r都会提供&a位阶&r,但每个都有其能设定的上限.\\n&7[位阶 sets the Enchantment Level which determines what Enchantments you can or will get! \\n\\nIt's default is 0 and max is 100. \\n\\nAlmost all Bookshelves will give 位阶 but each has max they can set it to.]&f"]
	quest.0F3A0A4DC18E5E55.title: "&a永恒&7[位阶]&f"
	quest.105442DA79829777.quest_desc: ["用8本&7书&r和一个铁砧,我们可以制作&8&a分解宝典&f&r.嗯,实际上是8本,但你明白意思!\\n\\n通过在铁砧中将一件物品与&8宝典&r结合,我们可以从物品上取下一半的&5附魔&r.\\n\\n这最终会导致物品在完成后损坏并消失.我不推荐使用它,你应该升级它!\\n&7[With 8 Books and an Anvil we can make the Tome of Scrapping. Well actually 8 of them, but you get the picture! \\n\\nBy combining an Item with the Tome in an Anvil, we can take half the Enchantments off the Item. \\n\\nThis will end up breaking and voiding the Item after it is done. I don't recommend using it, rather you should upgrade it!]&f"]
	quest.105442DA79829777.quest_subtitle: "一半附魔,损坏物品&7[Half Enchantments, breaks Items]&f"
	quest.105442DA79829777.title: "&8&a分解宝典&f&7[Tome of Scrapping]&f"
	quest.148A33CC36B2563A.quest_desc: ["&d龙息书架&r是我们完美设置所需的最后一个书架.\\n\\n它可能只提供&a位阶&r,但它拥有&a100&r的最大&a位阶&r值.\\n\\n要合成它,我们需要5个&3&a末影珍珠&f&r和一个&d龙首&r.这就是它被称为&d龙息&r的原因!\\n\\n要获得它们,你可以使用&a&lMA&r或在&d末地船&r上找到它们.&d末地船&r是&d&l末地&r中的结构,在船头(前端)有&d龙首&r.\\n&7[The Draconic Shelf is the last Shelf we'll need for perfect set up. \\n\\nIt might only give 位阶 but it has the max 位阶 of 100. \\n\\nTo Craft it we'll need 5 Ender Pearls and a Dragon Head. That is what makes it Draconic! \\n\\nTo get them you can either use lMA or find them on End Ships. End Ships are Structures in lThe End, on the bow (front) is the Dragon Head. ]&f"]
	quest.148A33CC36B2563A.title: "&d龙息末地书架&7[Draconic Endshelf]&f"
	quest.158F872A3A2C3650.quest_desc: ["现在我们有了&a80&r的最大&a位阶&r值,我们可以开始&d&l灌注&r&d龙息&r了!\\n\\n&d龙息&r可以在与&d&l&a末影龙&f&r战斗时获得.当她栖息在她的巢穴上方时,她可能会向你喷射&d粉色&r雾气.身处其中时,你可以用&a空瓶&f&a右击&f,以获得&d龙息&r!\\n\\n获得我们所需等级的最佳方式是使用4个&9回响幽匿书架&r、4个&9灵魂触感幽匿书架&r和6个&6稳定晶洞封装书架&r.\\n\\n这些将给我们&a80点永恒&r、&c25%量子&r和&5100%奥术&r.完美用于&d&l灌注&r!\\n&7[Now that we have our max 位阶 of 80, we can start lInfusing Dragon's Breath! \\n\\nDragon's Breath can be obtained when fighting the lEnder Dragon. When she is perched above her nest she might shoot a Pink mist at you. When in it, you can Right Click with an Empty Bottle, to obtain Dragon's Breath! \\n\\nThe best way to get our Levels is with 4 Echoing Sculkshelves, 4 Soul-Touched Sculkshelves, and 6 Geode-Encased Bookshelves of Stability. \\n\\nThese will give us 80 位阶, 25% 量子化 and 100% 阿卡那. Perfect for lInfusion!]&f"]
	quest.158F872A3A2C3650.title: "&d灌注龙息&7[Infused Dragon's Breath]&f"
	quest.1873205CF5247E3E.quest_desc: [
		"最后一个也是最伟大的&7书架&r,&d末地书架&r!\\n\\n这些是用6个&e&a末地石砖&f&r、1个&3&a末影珍珠&f&r、1个&7书架&r,当然还有&d灌注龙息&r制成的.\\n\\n它们目前的属性并不是最好的,每个只提供5点.但它们&a90&r的最大&a位阶&r值非常惊人!\\n\\n哦,对了,它们还可以用其他物品合成来升级!\\n&7[The last and greatest of the Bookshelves, the Endshelves! \\n\\nThese are created with 6 Endstone Bricks, 1 Ender Pearl, 1 Bookshelf, and of course the Infused Dragon's Breath. \\n\\nTheir stats aren't currently the best, only giving 5 for each. But their max 位阶 of 90 is incredible! \\n\\nOh yeah plus they can be Crafted with other Items to upgrade them!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/apothic/enchant_endshelf.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1873205CF5247E3E.title: "&d末地书架&7[Endshelves]&f"
	quest.191A7F3C9FBA4C13.quest_desc: ["我们可以用 &b海晶砂粒&r 合成 &b灌注海晶书架&r 来获得 &b晶化海晶书架&r.\\n\\n&b晶化海晶书架&r 将保持相同的 &a5 位阶&r、&5% 奥术值&r,并且现在拥有 &c3% 量子值&r.\\n\\n有了 12 个这样的书架,我们就能获得足够的等级来 &d&l灌注&r &9休眠深板岩书架&r,使其变成普通的 &9深板岩书架&r!\\n&7[We can Craft Infused Seashelves with Prismarine Crystals to get Crystalline Seashelves. \\n\\nThe Crystalline Seashelves will keep the same 5 位阶, 5% 阿卡那, and now have 3% 量子化. \\n\\nWith 12 of them, we can get enough Levels to lInfuse Dormant Deepshelves into normal Deepshelves!]&f"]
	quest.191A7F3C9FBA4C13.title: "&b晶化海晶书架&7[Crystalline Seashelf]&f"
	quest.1FAFDB20F504688E.quest_desc: ["&5附魔&r 在 &5&l&d神化&f&r 中有一些变化.\\n\\n简单来说,现在 15 个 &7书架&r 已经不够用了.\\n\\n现在有了新的书架,并且你可以对 &5&a附魔台&f&r 进行新的操作,希望这些任务能帮助你理解.\\n&7[Enchanting gets a few changes with lApotheosis. \\n\\nTo summarize it, 15 Bookshelves won't be enough now. \\n\\nThere's new Bookshelves and actions you can do with Enchantment Tables now and hopefully these quests will help you understand.]&f"]
	quest.1FAFDB20F504688E.title: "&5&l&d神化附魔&f&7[lApothic Enchanting]&f"
	quest.224716A537F2FFA0.quest_desc: ["&8盔甲魔典&r 用于获得只能用于盔甲的 &5附魔&r.所有 &8魔典&r 都能获得 &5保护&f、&5&a爆炸保护&f&f 和 &5&a火焰保护&f&r.\\n\\n每种魔典还会提供专属于盔甲特定部位的附魔.靴子会提供 &5&a深海探索者&f&r,头盔会提供 &5&a水下速掘&f&r.\\n\\n如果你只想最大概率获得 &5保护&r,试试 &8胸甲魔典&r 吧!\\n&7[Armor Tomes are used to get Enchantments which are only used on Armor. All of the Tomes can get Protection, Blast Protection, and Fire Protection. \\n\\nEach also gives ones reserved for a certain part of the Armor. Boots will give Depth Strider and Helmets will give Aqua Affinity. \\n\\nIf you want the best chance for just Protection try the Chestplate Tome!]&f"]
	quest.224716A537F2FFA0.title: "&8盔甲魔典&7[Armor Tomes]&f"
	quest.235E3C386E8D36A3.quest_desc: [
		"这就是 &4下界书架&r 和 &b海晶书架&r 分道扬镳的终点!\\n\\n首先,我们需要合成一个 &9休眠深板岩书架&r.这只需要 6 个 &8&a裂纹深板岩瓦&f&r 和 3 本 &7书&r.\\n\\n然后,我们需要 &a60 位阶&r、&c40% 量子值&r 和 &540% 奥术值&r.我们可以用 12 个 &b晶化海晶书架&r 或 12 个 &4发光下界书架&r 来获得!\\n\\n最后,我们可以 &d&l灌注&r 我们的 &9休眠深板岩书架&r,使其变成普通的 &9深板岩书架&r!\\n&7[This is where the separation of Hellshelves and Seashelves end! \\n\\nFirst, we'll need to Craft a Dormant Deepshelf. These are just 6 Cracked Deepslate Tiles and 3 Books. \\n\\nThen, we'll need 60 位阶, 40% 量子化, and 40% 阿卡那. We can get that with 12 Crystalline Seashelves or 12 Glowing Hellshelves! \\n\\nFinally, we can lInfuse our Dormant Deepshelves into regular Deepshelves!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/apothic/enchant_deepshelf.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.235E3C386E8D36A3.title: "&9深板岩书架&7[Deepshelf]&f"
	quest.24391162F4FF0587.quest_desc: ["在 &5附魔台&r 周围放置 15 个 &b海晶书架&r,我们就可以 &d&l灌注&r 最后一个 &b海晶书架&r 了!\\n\\n&b灌注海晶书架&r 提供更多的 &a位阶&r,为 5 点,最多可达 &a60&r 点.同时提供更多的 &5奥术值&r,为 &5%&r.\\n\\n这些可以合成为不同的 &7书架&r,我们正在寻找的、用于 &6最大化附魔&r 的是 &b晶化海晶书架&r.\\n\\n我们需要 12 个这样的书架,所以我们需要 12 个 &b灌注海晶书架&r.合成 8 个,剩下的我会奖励给你!\\n&7[With the 15 Seashelves around the Enchanting Table, we can lInfuse our last Seashelf! \\n\\nInfused Seashelves give more 位阶 at 5 with a max of 60. Also more 阿卡那 at 5%. \\n\\nThese can be Crafted into different Bookshelves, the ones we're looking for, for Max Enchanting is the Crystalline Seashelf. \\n\\nWe'll need 12 of those, so we'll need 12 Infused Seashelves. Craft 8 and I'll reward you the rest!]&f"]
	quest.24391162F4FF0587.title: "&b&a灌注海洋书架&f&7[Infused Seashelf]&f"
	quest.24C757B8AA6841F6.quest_desc: ["&5&l&d神化&f&r知道&3三叉戟&r有多难获取,所以让它变得更容易了……嗯,算是更容易吧!\\n\\n你现在可以制作一把&3&a惰性三叉戟&f&r,然后通过&d&l灌注&r来获得一把普通的&3三叉戟&r.\\n\\n&3三叉戟&r需要&a40 永恒&r、&c20%-50% 量子&r以及至少&535% 奥术&r.\\n\\n你可以用1个&7书架&r、4个&9回响幽匿书架&r和1个&2西瓜书架&r来达成这个条件.\\n&7[lApotheosis knows how annoying Tridents can be to get so they made it easier... well kinda easier! \\n\\nYou can now make an Inert Trident and lInfuse it to get a normal Trident. \\n\\nThe Trident requires between 40 位阶, 20%-50% 量子化, and atleast 35% 阿卡那. \\n\\nYou can get this with 1 Bookshelf, 4 Echoing Sculkshelf, and 1 Melonshelf.]&f"]
	quest.24C757B8AA6841F6.title: "制作真正的&3三叉戟&7[Making a real Trident]&f"
	quest.24FCFF18296ED907.quest_desc: ["要进一步升级&9深暗书架&r,令人惊讶的是,我们不需要&d&l灌注&r!相反,我们需要更多的合成!\\n\\n首先,需要4个&3幽匿块&r.你可以用&c下界合金&r筛网筛&e&a压纹末地石&f&r来获得它们.\\n\\n最后是&9监守者卷须&r和一个&3&a幽匿催发体&f&r……这些是&a掉落自&f&9&l监守者&r……是的,你需要杀死&9&l监守者&r.\\n\\n一旦你集齐所有材料,就可以合成最好的&7书架&r之一!一个能提供&a10 永恒&r、&c15% 量子&r和&510% 奥术&r的书架.\\n\\n最重要的是,它使我们的最大&a位阶&r达到&a80&r!几乎到100了!\\n&7[To upgrade Deepshelves even farther, surprisingly we don't need lInfusion! Instead we need more Crafting! \\n\\nFirst, is 4 Sculk Blocks. You can get these by sieving Crushed End Stone with a Netherite Mesh.\\n\\nLast is the Warden Tendril and a Sculk Catalyst... these are Drops from the lWarden... Yes, you'll need to kill the lWarden.\\n\\nOnce you have all that you can Craft one of the best Bookshelves! One that gives 10 位阶, 15% 量子化, and 10% 阿卡那. \\n\\nAnd most importantly, gives us a max 位阶 of 80! Almost to 100!]&f"]
	quest.24FCFF18296ED907.title: "&9灵魂触染幽匿书架&7[Soul-Touched Sculkshelf]&f"
	quest.2EC2FA680076C07D.quest_desc: ["要进一步升级&9深暗书架&r,令人惊讶的是,我们不需要&d&l灌注&r!相反,我们需要更多的合成!\\n\\n首先,需要4个&3幽匿块&r.你可以用&c下界合金&r筛网筛&e&a压纹末地石&f&r来获得它们.\\n\\n最后是&9监守者卷须&r和一个&3&a幽匿催发体&f&r……这些是&a掉落自&f&9&l监守者&r……是的,你需要杀死&9&l监守者&r.\\n\\n一旦你集齐所有材料,就可以合成最好的&7书架&r之一!一个能提供&a10 永恒&r、&c10% 量子&r和&515% 奥术&r的书架.\\n\\n最重要的是,它使我们的最大&a位阶&r达到&a80&r!几乎到100了!\\n&7[To upgrade Deepshelves even farther, surprisingly we don't need lInfusion! Instead we need more Crafting! \\n\\nFirst, is 4 Sculk Blocks. You can get these by sieving Crushed End Stone with a Netherite Mesh.\\n\\nLast is the Warden Tendril and a Sculk Catalyst... these are Drops from the lWarden... Yes, you'll need to kill the lWarden. \\n\\nOnce you have all that you can Craft one of the best Bookshelves! One that gives 10 位阶, 10% 量子化, and 15% 阿卡那. \\n\\nAnd most importantly, gives us a max 位阶 of 80! Almost to 100!]&f"]
	quest.2EC2FA680076C07D.title: "&9回响幽匿书架&7[Echoing Sculkshelf]&f"
	quest.31E7F7464D79F881.quest_desc: ["不只是&7书架&r可以被&d&l灌注&r!\\n&7[It's not just Bookshelves that can be lInfused!]&f"]
	quest.31E7F7464D79F881.title: "其他&d&l灌注&r物品&7[Other lInfusion Items]&f"
	quest.377D6CF86BC1C64F.quest_desc: ["&8&a分解宝典&f&r只会移除一半的&5附魔&r,而&8高级拆解宝典&r会移除物品上的所有&5附魔&r!\\n\\n不过,这两本&8宝典&r在使用时都会破坏物品.\\n\\n要将我们的&8&a分解宝典&f&r&d&l灌注&r成&8高级拆解宝典&r,我们可以使用3个&9回响幽匿书架&r和15个书架,或者4个&a龙块&f.\\n&7[The Tome of Scrapping will only take off half the Enchantments, while the Tome of Superior Scrapping will take every Enchantment off the Item! \\n\\nBoth of these Tomes will break the Item in use though. \\n\\nTo lInfuse our Tome of Scrapping into a Tome of Superior Scrapping we can use 3 Echoing Sculkshelves and 15 Bookshelves, or 4 Draconium Blocks.]&f"]
	quest.377D6CF86BC1C64F.quest_subtitle: "所有附魔,破坏物品&7[All Enchantments, breaks Item]&f"
	quest.377D6CF86BC1C64F.title: "&8高级拆解宝典&7[Tome of Superior Scrapping]&f"
	quest.3D31B94CC42BCE43.quest_desc: ["&8提取宝典&r正是我们寻找的&8宝典&r!它会移除所有&5附魔&r并且不损坏物品!\\n\\n要制作它,我们需要&d&l灌注&r我们的&8高级拆解宝典&r.\\n\\n我们可以直接使用之前的配置来完成.\\n&7[The Tome of Extraction is the Tome we are looking for! It will take off all Enchantments and leave the Item alone! \\n\\nTo make it we'll need to lInfuse our Tome of Superior Scrapping. \\n\\nWe can just use our previous setup for this.]&f"]
	quest.3D31B94CC42BCE43.quest_subtitle: "所有附魔,不破坏&7[All Enchantments, doesn't break]&f"
	quest.42746659C66CF17F.quest_desc: ["&6&o&a亚历山大图书馆&f&r是一个更好的&5&a附魔储备台&f&r.\\n\\n它可以存储更高级别的&5&a附魔书&f&r,但取出时仍然需要相应级别的&5书&r.\\n\\n它还能存储更多点数.&5&a附魔储备台&f&r可以存储32768点,而&6&o&a亚历山大图书馆&f&r可以存储每种&5书&r11亿点!\\n\\n要获得它,我们需要&d&l灌注&r&5&a附魔储备台&f&r.\\n\\n使用4个&9灵魂触染幽匿书架&f、4个&9回响幽匿书架&f、1个&d龙末书架&f、5个&6稳定晶洞书架&r和一个&a骷髅头颅&f.\\n&7[The Library of Alexandria is a better Enchantment Library. \\n\\nIt can hold higher Levels of Enchanted Books, but it will still need the Level of Book to get taken out at that Level. \\n\\nIt will also hold more Points. The Enchantment Library can hold 32768, while the Library of Alexandria can hold 1.1 Billion Points of each Book! \\n\\nTo obtain it, we'll need to lInfuse the Enchantment Library. \\n\\nUse 4 Soul-Touched Sculkshelves, 4 Echoing Sculkshelves, 1 Draconic Endshelf, 5 Geode-Encased Bookshelves of Stability, and a Skeleton Skull.]&f"]
	quest.42746659C66CF17F.quest_subtitle: "想象一下如果罗马从未被焚毁……&7[Just imagine if Rome never burned...]&f"
	quest.42746659C66CF17F.title: "&6&o&a亚历山大图书馆&f&7[Library of Alexandria]&f"
	quest.43167C59036E79A7.quest_desc: ["&8矿工宝典&r会帮助你进行所有采矿工作.它会提供&5效率&f、&5时运&f和&5&a精准采集&f&r.\\n\\n这些适用于镐、斧、锹,甚至锄头!\\n\\n&8&a渔夫宝典&f&r只会提供&a钓鱼竿&f的&5附魔&r,而且确实有很多.\\n&7[The Tome of Miners will help you with all your Mining. It will give Efficiency, Fortune, and Silk Touch. \\n\\nThese work for Pickaxes, Axes, Shovels, and even Hoes! \\n\\nTome of the Fishers will only give Fishing Rod Enchantments, and yeah there is a lot.]&f"]
	quest.43167C59036E79A7.title: "&8工具宝典&7[Tool Tomes]&f"
	quest.45161821C221EF0B.quest_desc: ["一旦我们在&5&a附魔台&f&r周围放置好那15个&4地狱书架&r,我们的&5附魔台&r就将拥有&a45 永恒&r和&c30% 量子&r.\\n\\n这是&d&l灌注&r我们的&4地狱书架&r的完美数值!\\n\\n&4灌注地狱书架&r提供&a5 永恒&r,最大&a位阶&r为&a60&r,同时提供&c5% 量子&r.\\n\\n这些可以与其他物品合成来制作不同的&7书架&r,对于我们想要的类型,我们需要12个&4灌注地狱书架&r!\\n\\n当然,我如此慷慨,你只需要收集8个!\\n&7[Once we get those 15 Hellshelves around our Enchantment Table, we'll have 45 位阶 and 30% 量子化 in our Table. \\n\\nThis is the perfect amount to lInfuse our Hellshelves! \\n\\nInfused Hellshelves give 5 位阶 with a max of 60 位阶, along with 5% 量子化. \\n\\nThese can be Crafted with other Items to make different Bookshelves, for the ones we want we'll need 12 Infused Hellshelves! \\n\\nOf course, with me being soooo generous, you'll only need to collect 8!]&f"]
	quest.45161821C221EF0B.title: "&4灌注地狱书架&7[Infused Hellshelves]&f"
	quest.4E895C54651A3CB3.quest_desc: ["&8宝典&r就是&7书&r……只是更有用的&7书&r!\\n\\n每本&8宝典&r都用&7书&r、木棍、&c&a烈焰棒&f&f和&c火药&r合成.\\n\\n&8宝典&r可以像物品一样被&5附魔&r,以获得特定的&5附魔&r.\\n\\n还有&8拆解宝典&r,可以在铁砧上使用来移除物品上的&5附魔&r.\\n&7[Tomes are Books... just more useful Books! \\n\\nEach Tome is Crafted with Books, Sticks, Blaze Rods and Powder. \\n\\nTomes can be Enchanted, like Items, to get certain Enchantments. \\n\\nThere is also the Tomes of Scrapping which can be used in Anvils to take Enchantments off Items.]&f"]
	quest.4E895C54651A3CB3.title: "&8&l宝典&7[lTomes]&f"
	quest.516E66BE01EE5B31.quest_desc: ["&8武器宝典&r会提供剑和斧的&5附魔&r.\\n\\n主要是那些有助于杀戮的!比如&5锋利&f和&5&a火焰附加&f&r.\\n&8箭术宝典&r会提供远程武器的&5附魔&r,即弓和弩.\\n\\n&5穿透&f、&5力量&f和&5击退&r!\\n&7[Tomes of Weaponry will give Enchantments for Swords and Axes. \\n\\nMostly the ones that help with Killing things! Like Sharpness and Fire Aspect. \\nTomes of Archery will give Enchantments for ranged Weapons, the Bow and Crossbow. \\n\\nPiercing, Power, and Knockback!]&f"]
	quest.516E66BE01EE5B31.title: "&8武器宝典&7[Weapon Tomes]&f"
	quest.51E554305FFEBA1D.quest_desc: ["&4炽焰地狱书架&r提供一点&c量子&r和&a位阶&r,但它们不是我们为&d&l灌注&r寻找的廉价选择!\\n&7[Blazing Hellshelves give a bit of 量子化 and 位阶 but they aren't the cheap option we are looking for, for our lInfusions!]&f"]
	quest.51E554305FFEBA1D.title: "&4炽焰地狱书架&7[Blazing Hellshelf]&f"
	quest.523DC411241B470A.quest_desc: [
		"&5&a附魔台&f&r的所有&5附魔&r都由&a位阶&r、&c量子&r和&5阿卡那&r的等级决定.\\n\\n我们可以在物品被&5附魔&r时,点击&5&a附魔台&f&r GUI &a右上角&f的？来查看可用的&5附魔&r池.\\n\\n&c量子&r越高,我们获得较弱&5附魔&r的几率就越大.\\n\\n使用&6稳定晶洞书架&r可以消除较差&5附魔&r几率增加的效果.\\n&7[All Enchantments from the Enchantment Table is determined by the Levels of 位阶, 量子化, and 阿卡那. \\n\\nWe can see the Pool of Enchantments available by clicking the ? in the Top Right of the Enchantment Table's GUI when an Item is being Enchanted. \\n\\nThe higher the 量子化 is, the better the chance we get a weaker Enchantment gets. \\n\\nWith the Geode-Encased Bookshelf of Stability it will get rid of the increased chances of worse Enchantments.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"要合成它,我们需要一个&7书架&r、7个方解石和1个&5&a紫水晶母岩&f&r.\\n\\n&5&a紫水晶母岩&f&r无法通过挖掘获得,即使使用&5&a精准采集&f&r也不行.你需要通过仪式、灌注或&c&l熔铸炉&r来获得一个!\\n&7[To Craft it we'll need a Bookshelf, 7 Calcite, and 1 Budding Amethyst. \\n\\nBudding Amethyst can not be collected from Mining, even with Silk Touch. You'll need either a Ritual, Infusion, or a lFoundry to get one then!]&f"
	]
	quest.523DC411241B470A.title: "&6移除负面附魔&7[Negative Enchantments Removal]&f"
	quest.586D5DE28EEC8014.quest_desc: ["&c量子&r有助于混合&5附魔&r池,使得更容易获得一大堆不同的&5附魔&r.\\n\\n不过,&c量子&r也可能对你不利,你拥有的越多,较弱的&5附魔&r就越常见.\\n\\n以前我们使用&e矫正&r,但现在我们使用&6稳定晶洞书架&r!\\n\\n默认&c量子&r为&c15%&r,其最大值为&c100%&r.\\n&7[量子化 helps to mix up the Enchantment Pool, making it easier to get a whole bunch of different Enchantments. \\n\\n量子化 can work against you though, the more you have it, the more common weaker Enchantments will get.\\n\\nBefore we used Rectification, instead we now use Geode-Encased Bookshelves of Stability! \\n\\nDefault 量子化 is 15% and its max is 100%.]&f"]
	quest.586D5DE28EEC8014.title: "&c量子&7[量子化]&f"
	quest.5C73247A48E72FB3.quest_desc: ["如果你想&a移除&f&5附魔池&r中的特定&5附魔&r,你可以在&5附魔&r设置中使用这个&b书架&r!\\n\\n将一个你想要加入黑名单的&5附魔书&r放入这个&b海洋书架&r的空位中.\\n\\n然后,当你&5附魔&r时,这个&5附魔&r就不会出现在物品或书上了.\\n&7[If you want to remove a specific Enchant from Enchantment Pool, you can use this Bookshelf in your Enchanting set up! \\n\\nPlace an Enchantment Book, you want to Blacklist, in an empty spot in this Seashelf. \\n\\nThen, when you Enchant, this Enchantment won't show up on Items or Books.]&f"]
	quest.5C73247A48E72FB3.title: "从池中移除&5附魔&r&7[Remove Enchantments from Pool]&f"
	quest.5DE45BC0258D1B0B.quest_desc: ["&d珍珠末书架&r是一个不错的&7书架&r,尤其是考虑到它的价格.\\n\\n它由&d末书架&r与4个&7&a末地烛&f&r和2个&3&a末影珍珠&f&r组合而成.\\n\\n它会使我们的最大&a位阶&r达到&a90&r,但这并不是我们追求的最大&5附魔&r效果.\\n&7[The Pearlescent Endshelf is an alright Shelf especially for the price. \\n\\nIt is created by combining an Endshelf with 4 End Rods and 2 Ender Pearls. \\n\\nIt will give us max 位阶 90, but this isn't what we want for max Enchanting.]&f"]
	quest.5DE45BC0258D1B0B.title: "&d珍珠末书架&7[Pearlescent Endshelf]&f"
	quest.60850E717C747A78.quest_desc: ["你有没有花3个月研究&o银河代码&r,最终理解&5&a附魔台&f&r的语言,结果发现它全是胡言乱语？\\n\\n没有？\\n\\n我也没有,但&9附魔线索&r是它真正的翻译器!\\n\\n每个&9附魔线索&r会在你实际使用前告诉你1个&5附魔&r.\\n&7[You ever spend 3 months studying Galactic Code to finally understand Enchantment Table language just for it to be gibberish? \\n\\nNo? \\n\\nMe either, but Enchanting Clues are your actual translator for it! \\n\\nEach Enchanting Clue will tell you 1 Enchantment before you actually use it.]&f"]
	quest.60850E717C747A78.title: "&3附魔线索&7[Enchanting Clues]&f"
	quest.61217D80BFF8A858.quest_desc: ["第三级也是最后一级的&5&a末影拴绳&f&r来了!这个是不可破坏的,甚至可以将生物绑定到刷怪笼上.它需要一个相当&a狡猾&f的&d&l灌注&r设置.我们至少需要&a75 永恒&r、&c85% 量子&r以及&560-85% 奥术&r.\\n\\n你可以用4个&9灵魂触染幽匿书架&r、4个&9回响幽匿书架&r、2个&7石书架&r和一个原版书架来达成.哦,你还需要一个女巫在用于这次&d&l灌注&r的&a末影拴绳&f里.\\n&7[The third and final tier of Ender Lead is here! This one is unbreakable and can even bind mobs to Spawners. It will require a considerably more tricky lInfusion setup. We'll need at least 75 位阶, 85% 量子化, and between 60-85% 阿卡那.\\n\\nYou can get this with 4 Soul-Touched Sculkshelves, 4 Echoing Sculkshelves, 2 Stoneshelves, and a vanilla Bookshelf. Oh, and you also need a Witch in the Ender Lead used for this lInfusion.]&f"]
	quest.61217D80BFF8A858.quest_subtitle: "我发誓这和&d神秘学&f无关&7[Nothing to do with Occultism I swear]&f"
	quest.61217D80BFF8A858.title: "&5神秘 &a末影拴绳&f&7[Occult Ender Lead]&f"
	quest.6220EDE42C813C1B.quest_desc: ["&e护符&r最糟糕的地方就是它们会损坏!为什么这些强力的&a药水效果&f必须有耐久度!\\n\\n不过别担心,&5&l&d神化&f&r有办法解决……通过&d&l灌注&r!\\n\\n你需要&a100 永恒&r、&c8.5%&f到&c13.5% 量子&r以及&532.5%&f到&537.5% 奥术&r.\\n\\n你可以使用10个&4发光地狱书架&r、4个&6稳定晶洞书架&r、2个&d龙末书架&r和一个&a骷髅头颅&f!\\n\\n是的,除了&7书架&r,一些头颅和其他物品也提供属性!\\n&7[The worst part about Charms is that they break! Why would these OP Potion Effects have to have Durability! \\n\\nWell don't you worry, lApotheosis has a cure for that... with lInfusions! \\n\\nYou'll need 100 位阶, between 8.5% and 13.5% 量子化, and between 32.5% and 37.5% 阿卡那. \\n\\nYou can use 10 Glowing Hellshelves, 4 Geode-Encased Bookshelves of Stability, 2 Draconic Endshelves, and a Skeleton Skull! \\n\\nYes, some Skulls and other Items besides Bookshelves give stats!]&f"]
	quest.6220EDE42C813C1B.title: "不可破坏的&e护符&7[Unbreakable Charms]&f"
	quest.62D39F68DE6E44A4.quest_desc: ["&5阿卡那&r是非常重要的量,它增加你获得的&5附魔&r数量；并使稀有&5附魔&r更常见.\\n\\n以剑为例,&5亡灵杀手&r是一个非常常见的&5附魔&r,但&5抢夺&r则稀有得多.\\n\\n&5阿卡那&r的默认值是&50%&r,最大值是&5100%&r.\\n&7[阿卡那 is very important quantity, it increases the amount of Enchantments you get; and makes rare Enchantments more common. \\n\\nAn example with Swords would be like, Smite is a very common Enchantment but Looting is much more rare. \\n\\n阿卡那s default is 0% and max is 100%.]&f"]
	quest.62D39F68DE6E44A4.title: "&5奥术&7[阿卡那]&f"
	quest.6852BEFDD4DE4E4B.quest_desc: ["&9灵魂触染深暗书架&r是&9深暗书架&r的升级版.\\n\\n它们用一个&b&a灵魂灯笼&f&r和3个&3幽匿块&r合成.你需要用&c下界合金&r筛网筛&e&a压纹末地石&f&r.\\n\\n然后,我们就可以合成我们的&9灵魂触染&r版本.这些会提供多得多的&c量子&r,达到&c15%&r!\\n\\n它还将最大&a位阶&r增加到&a75&r.\\n&7[Soul-Touched Deepshelves are an upgrade to Deepshelves. \\n\\nThey are Crafted with a Soul Lantern and 3 Sculk Blocks. You'll need to sieve Crushed End Stone with a Netherite Mesh.\\n\\nThen, we can Craft our Soul-Touched version. These will give a ton more 量子化 at 15%! \\n\\nIt also increases max 位阶 to 75.]&f"]
	quest.6852BEFDD4DE4E4B.title: "&9灵魂触染深暗书架&7[Soul-Touched Deepshelf]&f"
	quest.6884E25641A1020C.quest_desc: ["&5&a附魔储备台&f&r 是有史以来最棒的 &5&a附魔书&f&r 存储设备!\\n\\n要合成它,你需要 4 个 &3&a末影箱子&f&r、1 个 &5附魔台&r 和 4 个任何 &d&l灌注&r 过的 &7书架&r:&4&a灌注下界书架&f&r、&b灌注海晶书架&r 和 &9深板岩书架&r.\\n\\n要使用它,你可以按住 Shift 键 &a左击&f &5&a附魔书&f&r 或将它们放入 &9蓝色槽位&r.这会将 &5附魔书&r 添加到 &5图书馆&r 中.\\n\\n&5附魔书&r 按名称排序,并以点数形式存储.&5&a附魔书&f&r 的每个等级决定了其等级,并反映在获得该等级所需的 &5附魔书&r 数量上.等级 1 需要 1 点.等级 2 需要 2 点.等级 3 需要 4 点.等级 4 需要 8 点.\\n\\n每种 &5附魔书&r 最多可存储 32768 点,可以通过 &a左击&f 已存储的 &5附魔书&r 来提取.每次点击都会为 &6橙色槽位&r 中的 &5附魔书&r 增加一个等级.\\n\\n你可以点击不同的 &5附魔书&r 来添加到 &6橙色槽位&r 中的 &5附魔书&r 上,类似于在铁砧中合并 &5附魔书&r.\\n\\n&5&a附魔书&f&r 的最高等级取决于你放入的最高等级 &5附魔书&r.即使你有 32000 点,如果你只放入了 &5锋利 III&r,你也只能取出 &5锋利 III&r.\\n&7[The Enchantment Library is the single greatest Enchanted Book storage, ever! \\n\\nTo Craft it you'll need 4 Ender Chests, 1 Enchanting Table, and 4 of any of the lInfused Bookshelves: Infused Hellshelf, Infused Seashelves, and Deepshelves. \\n\\nTo use it, you can either Shift Left Click Enchanted Books or bring them into the Blue Slot. This will add the Books to the Library. \\n\\nThe Books are sorted by name and are held in Points. Each Level of Enchanted Book determines the Level, and it is reflected on how many Books would be needed to get that Level. Level 1, is 1 Point. Level 2 is 2 Points. Level 3 is 4 Points. Level 4 is 8 Points. \\n\\nEach Book is stored to a max of 32768 Points, and they can be extracted by Left Clicking the stored Book. Each Click will add another Level to the Book in the Orange Slot. \\n\\nYou can Click different Books to add to the Book in the Orange Slot, similar to combining Books in an Anvil. \\n\\nThe max Level of Enchanted Book is determined by the highest Level of Book you've put in. It doesn't matter if you have 32000 Points, if you only put in Sharpness III, you can only take out Sharpness III.]&f"]
	quest.6884E25641A1020C.title: "&5&a附魔储备台&f&7[Enchantment Library]&f"
	quest.695889817162EFC7.quest_desc: ["&a经验值&r 对于 &5&l&d神化&f 附魔&r 非常重要!每个 &5附魔&r 都需要它!(不然你以为我为什么在每个奖励中都给你？)\\n\\n通过 &d&l灌注&r,我们可以将 &6&a蜂蜜瓶&f&r 转化为 &a附魔之瓶&r.实际上,我们为此获得了 3 种不同的 &d&l灌注&r 配方!从 1 个 &a附魔之瓶&r,到 8 个,再到 32 个!\\n\\n第一种,是 1 个 &a附魔之瓶&r,只需要 2 个 &9回响幽匿书架&r.\\n\\n第二种,是 8 个 &a附魔之瓶&r,需要 5 个 &9回响幽匿书架&r 和 1 个 &9灵魂触感幽匿书架&r.\\n\\n最后一种,是 32 个 &a附魔之瓶&r,需要 5 个 &9回响幽匿书架&f、3 个 &9灵魂触感幽匿书架&f 和 1 个 &d龙息末地书架&r!\\n&7[EXP is very important for lApotheosis Enchanting! Every Enchant requires it! (Why do you think I give it in every Reward?) \\n\\nWith lInfusion we can transform Honey Bottles into Bottles O' Enchanting. Actually we get 3 different lInfusions for it! It goes from 1 Bottle O' Enchanting, to 8, to 32! \\n\\nFirst, is for 1 Bottle and needs only 2 Echoing Sculkshelves. \\n\\nSecond, is for 8 Bottles and needs 5 Echoing Sculkshelves and 1 Soul-Touched Sculkshelf. \\n\\nLast, is for 32 Bottles O' Enchanting and will need 5 Echoing Sculkshelves, 3 Soul-Touched, and 1 Draconic Endshelf!]&f"]
	quest.695889817162EFC7.title: "合成 &a经验值&r？&7[Crafting EXP?]&f"
	quest.6A07D09831428CB9.quest_desc: [
		"&4&l&a下界&f&r 可能相当可怕,如果你更愿意在 &b海洋&r 中航行,那就使用 &b海晶书架&r 吧!\\n\\n&b海晶书架&r 是你接触 &5奥术值&r 的入门,它们提供 &53% 奥术值&r 和 &a3 位阶&r.\\n\\n比普通的 &7书架&r 更好,对吧？\\n\\n你需要 16 个来进行 &d&l灌注&r……嗯,15 个用于 &d&l灌注&r,1 个被 &d&l灌注&r!\\n\\n就像 &4下界书架&r 一样,我会额外给你一些,现在先收集 11 个吧!\\n&7[lThe Nether can be pretty scary, if you'd rather voyage the Sea, use Seashelves! \\n\\nSeashelves are your introduction to 阿卡那, they give 3% 阿卡那 and 3 位阶. \\n\\nBetter than normal Shelves right? \\n\\nYou're going to need 16 for lInfusing... well 15 for lInfusing, 1 to be lInfused! \\n\\nLike the Hellshelves, I'll give you extra, just collect 11 now!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/apothic/enchant_seashelf.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6A07D09831428CB9.title: "&b海洋书架&7[Seashelves]&f"
	quest.6C2C135B9B7B9402.quest_desc: ["&d&l神化&r是&5附魔&r的一种特殊形式,讽刺的是,它用于获得更好的&5附魔&r.\\n\\n当达到足够的&a位阶&r、&c量子&r和&5阿卡那&r时,&5附魔&r将提供&d&l神化&r选项.\\n\\n(要了解所需等级,你可以查看EMI或跟随这些任务)\\n&7[lInfusion is a special version of Enchanting which ironically is used for better Enchantments. \\n\\nWhen the right amount of 位阶, 量子化, and 阿卡那 is reached the Enchantments will offer lInfusion. \\n\\n(To know the Levels needed you can check EMI or follow these Quests)]&f"]
	quest.6C2C135B9B7B9402.title: "&l&d神化&7[lInfusing]&f"
	quest.6C57D64518FF22C0.quest_desc: ["其余的&5附魔&r来自这本&8魔典&r.\\n\\n&5耐久&r……其他的我真不知道了……\\n&7[The rest of the Enchantments come from this Tome. \\n\\nUnbreaking... I don't really know what else...]&f"]
	quest.6C57D64518FF22C0.title: "&8其他魔典&7[ETC. Tomes]&f"
	quest.70D2C5FAC661E01A.quest_desc: ["&b心铸海洋书架&r是&b&a灌注海洋书架&f&r的又一次升级.\\n\\n它有点贵,但能提供大量的&5阿卡那&r!\\n\\n这对后期需要大量&5阿卡那&r的&d&l神化&r非常有帮助.\\n&7[The Heart-Forged Seashelf is another upgrade to the Infused Seashelf. \\n\\nIt's a little expensive but gives lots of 阿卡那! \\n\\nThis will be very helpful for later lInfusions needing lots of 阿卡那.]&f"]
	quest.70D2C5FAC661E01A.title: "&b心铸海洋书架&7[Heart-Forged Seashelf]&f"
	quest.784466C3813AA506.quest_desc: ["曾经想捕捉生物吗？我们有灵魂宝石、&a生物捕捉工具&f和生物捕捉器.\\n\\n我们暂时忽略那些,专注于&5&l&d神化&f&r提供的选项.&5脆弱的&a末影拴绳&f&r是&5&a末影拴绳&f&r中最便宜的变体,但也是最弱、最易碎的.它只能容纳动物,并在使用8次后损坏.\\n&7[Ever wanted to pick up mobs? We...have Soul Gems, Mob Imprisonment Tools, and Creature Catchers for that.\\n\\nLet's just ignore those for now and focus on the option lApotheosis offers. The Flimsy Ender Lead is the cheapest variant of Ender Lead, but also the weakest, and most fragile. It can only hold animals, and breaks after 8 uses.]&f"]
	quest.784466C3813AA506.title: "&5脆弱的&a末影拴绳&f&7[Flimsy Ender Lead]&f"
	quest.78BFDD3A9B996655.quest_desc: ["这是&5脆弱的&a末影拴绳&f&r的一个显著升级.现在,它也能容纳敌对生物,并且会在使用64次后损坏.要获得这个,我们至少需要&a45永恒&r、&c25%量子&r和&540%奥秘&r.\\n\\n这可以通过9个&b水晶海洋书架&r实现,或者,如果你更喜欢&4地狱书架&r,可以用9个&4发光地狱书架&r和8根蜡烛(提示:一个方块内最多可以放置4根蜡烛)\\n&7[A considerable step up from the Flimsy Ender Lead. Now, it can hold hostile mobs as well, and will break after 64 uses. To get this, we will need at least 45 位阶, 25% 量子化, and 40% 阿卡那.\\n\\nThis can be achieved with 9 Crystalline Seashelves, or, if you prefer Hellshelves, 9 Glowing Hellshelves and 8 Candles (Tip: You can fit up to 4 candles into one block)]&f"]
	quest.78BFDD3A9B996655.title: "&5&a末影拴绳&f&7[Ender Lead]&f"
	quest.78E66F1DE42C747A.quest_desc: ["&9&a回响碎片&f&r的获取可能相当烦人,而且我们需要很多!所以为什么不找一个更简单的获取方法呢？\\n\\n通过&d&l神化&r,我们可以将1个&9&a回响碎片&f&r变成4个!\\n\\n我们需要&a70永恒&r、&c50%量子&r和&50%奥秘&r.\\n\\n要达到这个,我们可以使用12个&4发光地狱书架&r和2个非&9休眠&r的&9深暗书架&r!\\n&7[Echo Shards can be pretty annoying to farm, plus we'll need a lot of them! So why not have an easier way of Farming them. \\n\\nWith lInfusion we can make 1 Echo Shard into 4! \\n\\nWe'll need 70 位阶, 50% 量子化, and 50% 阿卡那. \\n\\nTo get that, we can use 12 Glowing Hellshelves and 2 Deepshelves, that aren't Dormant!]&f"]
	quest.78E66F1DE42C747A.title: "无限的&9&a回响碎片&f&r？&7[Infinite Echo Shards?]&f"
	quest.78FEDE6FA4845585.quest_desc: ["有些&d&l神化&r需要非常、非常精确的&a位阶&r、&c量子&r或&5阿卡那&r数量.\\n\\n要获得这些,你可能需要这些&7书架&r中的一个.\\n\\n每个都会降低其对应属性的数值.\\n&7[Some lInfusions need very, very exact amounts of 位阶, 量子化, or 阿卡那. \\n\\nTo get these you might need one of these Shelves. \\n\\nEach lowers the amount of its respective quantities.]&f"]
	quest.78FEDE6FA4845585.title: "&4负值&r数量&7[Negative amounts]&f"
	quest.79AF63E77AD70A93.quest_desc: ["&7书架&r是你的起点,但绝对不是你的终点.至少不是普通的&7书架&r.\\n\\n仅使用普通&7书架&r,你只能将&a位阶&r提升到最高30.\\n(我很快会解释&5附魔等级&r,但要知道你需要提升它们)\\n&7[Bookshelves are your starting point, but definitely not your end point. Atleast not normal Bookshelves. \\n\\nWith only normal Bookshelves you can only get 位阶 up and to a max of 30. \\n(I will explain the Enchantment Levels soon but just know you need them up)]&f"]
	quest.79AF63E77AD70A93.title: "&2&l原版&r上限只是开始&7[lVanilla Max is just the start]&f"
	quest.7C758209D06ED0E3.quest_desc: ["通过将一个&4&a灌注下界书架&f&r与一些&e荧石&r结合,我们可以制作&4发光地狱书架&r!\\n\\n它们具有相同的&a位阶&r和&c量子&r,但提供&53%奥秘&r.\\n\\n这对后期的&d&l神化&r很有帮助,比如如果我们想用12个来&d&l神化&r一个&9休眠深暗书架&f成一个&9深暗书架&r!\\n&7[By combining an Infused Hellshelf with some Glowstone we can make Glowing Hellshelves! \\n\\nThese have the same 位阶 and 量子化, but give 3% 阿卡那. \\n\\nThis will be helpful in later lInfusions, like if we wish to use 12 of them to lInfuse a Dormant Deepshelf into a Deepshelf!]&f"]
	quest.7C758209D06ED0E3.title: "&4发光地狱书架&7[Glowing Hellshelf]&f"
	quest.7C9D9D1C054874A7.quest_desc: ["曾经想要最完美的&5附魔&r吗？比如,每个属性都最大化,每个好的&5附魔&r都可用？那么,你需要这些!\\n\\n首先,是5个&9灵魂触感幽匿书架&r和5个&9回响幽匿书架&r.这些将为我们提供所有需要的&c量子&r和&5阿卡那&r!\\n\\n接下来是&d龙息末地书架&r,它将为我们提供&a100永恒&r,即&a位阶&r的数量和最高等级.\\n\\n第三是&6晶洞封装稳定书架&r,这将确保&c量子&r不会用糟糕的&5附魔&r背刺我们!\\n\\n最后一个是可选的,但你应该加上它,&6奥秘宝藏深暗书架&r.那个&7书架&r将允许我们获得通常无法获得的&5附魔&r,比如&5经验修补&r!\\n&7[Ever want the most perfect Enchantments? Like, every stat maxed out, every good Enchantment available? Then, you'll need these! \\n\\nFirst, is the 5 Soul-Touched Sculkshelves and 5 Echoing Sculkshelves. These will give us all the 量子化 and 阿卡那 we need! \\n\\nNext, is the Draconic Endshelf which will give us 100 位阶, as in amount of 位阶 and the max level. \\n\\nThird, is the Geode-Encased Bookshelf of Stability, this will make it so the 量子化 doesn't backstab us with awful Enchantments! \\n\\nLast is optional but you should add it, the Deepshelf of Arcane Treasures. That Bookshelf will allow us to get Enchantments we normally wouldn't, like Mending!]&f"]
	quest.7C9D9D1C054874A7.title: "&6&l最佳附魔配置&7[lBest Enchanting set-up]&f"
	task.3D62C020980A2DEC.title: "书架&7[Bookshelves]&f"
	task.432FCFECDAA542F1.title: "书架&7[Bookshelves]&f"
	task.4644C76CEC129AA4.title: "永久护符&7[Permanent Charms]&f"
	task.52C6DC68BF096122.title: "武器魔典&7[Weapon Tomes]&f"
	task.598F1FCB5B5ED8FC.title: "工具魔典&7[Tool Tomes]&f"
	task.5AB4C41B6800D7FA.title: "盔甲魔典&7[Armor Tomes]&f"
	quest.00611844AFD5C31E.quest_desc: ["虽然压印器和充能器本身接受RF/FE,但ME网络的大部分使用其专用的能源系统,称为AE.\\n\\nRF/FE可以以2:1 RF:AE的比例转换为原生AE,可以直接通过&aME控制器&f,或者通过&b&a能源接收器&f&f,后者可以连接到网络的任何部分.\\n&7[While the Inscriber and Charger will natively accept RF/FE, the vast majority of an ME network uses its own dedicated power system called AE.\\n\\nRF/FE can be converted into the native AE at a ratio of 2:1 RF:AE, either directly through an ME Controller, or through the Energy Acceptor, which can instead be connected to any part of the network.]&f"]
	quest.00611844AFD5C31E.quest_subtitle: "接入电源&7[Plug in]&f"
	quest.01F3F0C25BA72BDA.quest_desc: [
		"除了物品和流体的存储,AE2还提供了一种原生方式,将整个&e结构&f存储在存储元件中,与&d更多空间/压缩空间&f模组并无太大不同.\\n&7[Aside from the storage of items and fluids, AE2 also provides a native way of storing entire structures inside of storage cells, not too dissimilarly to the Compact Machines mod. ]&f"
		""
		"&b&a空间IO端口&f&f允许将包含在&b空间容纳结构&f内的结构捕获到专门设计的存储元件中,通过红石信号激活.\\n&7[The Spatial IO Port allows structures contained within a Spatial Containment Structure to be captured within a specially-designed storage cell, activated via a redstone signal. ]&f"
		""
		"如果生物或玩家恰好在空间被捕获时站在SCS内,他们也会被传送到空间其余部分去的地方,即一个专用维度.只要确保如果你是那个被捕获的人,有办法进出.\\n&7[If a mob or player happens to stand inside of the SCS while the space is being captured, they too will be transported to where the rest of the space goes, i.e. in a dedicated dimension. Just make sure you have a way to get back out and in if you're the one being captured.]&f"
	]
	quest.01F3F0C25BA72BDA.title: "空间IO&7[Spatial IO]&f"
	quest.037488EF1F3581CE.quest_desc: ["默认情况下,没有&aME控制器&f的ME网络自身只有800AE的内部缓冲,控制器每方块额外增加8kAE.对于足够大的网络,这可能不足,并可能导致网络在尝试为任何连接的设备补充能量时间歇性断电.\\n\\n&b&a能源元件&f&f允许ME网络容纳显著更多的能量,每个普通&a能源元件&f增加200kAE,每个&b致密&f &a能源元件&f增加1.6MAE.这些也可以放置在网络中的任何位置以提供增加的能量缓冲.\\n&7[By default, an ME network on its own only has an internal buffer of 800AE without an ME Controller, with the controller adding an extra 8kAE per block. For large enough networks, this can be insufficient and may cause a network to power off intermittently when trying to recoup power for any connected devices.\\n\\nThe Energy Cell allows for an ME network to hold significantly more energy, adding another 200kAE per regular Energy Cell and 1.6MAE per Dense Energy Cell. These can also be placed anywhere in the network to provide the increased energy buffer.]&f"]
	quest.03E6FA4DCB71162E.quest_desc: ["&b&a染色器&f&f是一种可充电的工具,允许在世界中对线缆进行染色.它或多或少像一个专门的&e存储元件&f,可以装入原版染料或&e颜料球&f以获得特定颜色,以及&e雪球&f来洗掉颜色并将线缆变回其福鲁伊克斯变体.\\n\\n对线缆应用颜色会从其内部电池消耗100AE能量,单次充电总共可染色3400个线缆段.\\n&7[The Color Applicator is a chargeable tool that allows for in-world dyeing of cables. It functions more or less as a specialised storage cell to be loaded up with either vanilla dyes or paint balls for specific colours, along with snowballs to wash colours off and turn cables back to their Fluix variant.\\n\\nApplying colour to a cable uses 100AE of energy from its internal battery, for a total of 3400 cable segments in a single charge.]&f"]
	quest.03E6FA4DCB71162E.title: "&a染色器&f&7[Color Applicator]&f"
	quest.083D458032F0325C.quest_desc: ["&bME输出总线&f会定期将其白名单过滤器中的物品吐出到总线所面向的任何外部存储.与输入总线不同,输出总线必须设置过滤器才能工作.\\n&7[The ME Export Bus periodically spits items in its whitelist filter out to whatever external storage the bus is facing. Unlike the Import Bus, the Export Bus cannot work without being filtered.]&f"]
	quest.083D458032F0325C.quest_subtitle: "输出&7[The O]&f"
	quest.0B218DD73FE8D985.quest_desc: ["如果你正确完成了上一个任务,你应该已经将那个奇点变成了一对&b量子纠缠奇点&f.这些新的奇点用于连接一个称为&e量子网络桥&f的环形设备.\\n\\n当两个单独的环使用量子纠缠奇点连接并用一些AE能量(例如一个能源元件)启动后,ME网络可以在桥的另一端无线扩展,跨越长距离甚至维度.\\n&7[If you did that last quest correctly, you should have turned that singularity into a pair of Quantum Entangled Singularities. These new singularities are used to link together a ring-shaped device known as a Quantum Network Bridge.\\n\\nWhen two of these individual rings have been linked using the Quantum Entangled Singularities and jumpstarted with some AE power (e.g. an energy cell), an ME network can be expanded wirelessly on the other side of the bridge, across either long distances or even dimensions.]&f"]
	quest.0B218DD73FE8D985.title: "量子网络桥&7[Quantum Network Bridge]&f"
	quest.0E809747193ED3A9.quest_desc: ["第三级的MEGA存储组件,提供&e16777216&f(16384k)字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The third MEGA tier of storage component, providing 16777216 (16384k) bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.0E809747193ED3A9.quest_subtitle: "x4^2&7[x4^2]&f"
	quest.0E809747193ED3A9.title: "16M存储组件&7[16M Storage Component]&f"
	quest.0F03E75CF79BADD7.quest_desc: ["&aMEGA存储单元&f&f提供了定制的&b批量物品&a存储单元&f&f,每个单元最多只能存储&o一种&r物品类型,但可以存储几乎&o&l无限&r*数量的该物品类型.在它能接受一种物品类型之前,必须使用&a元件工作台&f预先设置过滤器.\\n\\n*&o技术上来说是”最大长整型”.如果你懂,你就懂.&r\\n&7[MEGA Cells offers the bespoke Bulk Item Storage Cell, which is limited to no more than one type of item storable per cell but can store a practically lINFINITE* number of that item type. Before it can accept an item type, it must be filtered in advance using a Cell Workbench.\\n\\n*Technically \"max long\". If you know, you know.]&f"]
	quest.0F03E75CF79BADD7.quest_subtitle: "批量与切割&7[Bulk and cut]&f"
	quest.0F03E75CF79BADD7.title: "批量物品存储&7[Bulk Item Storage]&f"
	quest.1348995F64A94396.quest_desc: ["&b合成监控器&f显示正在合成的总体物品,以及该物品仍在合成的剩余数量.\\n\\n基础AE2监控器和MEGA监控器功能相同,但出于美观目的提供.\\n&7[The Crafting Monitor displays the overall item being crafted, along with the remaining quantity of that item still being crafted.\\n\\nBoth the base AE2 monitor and the MEGA monitor function identically, but are provided for aesthetic purposes.]&f"]
	quest.1348995F64A94396.quest_subtitle: "下载更多显存&7[Download more VRAM]&f"
	quest.140DE53DC0FCD9F4.quest_desc: [
		"&b&aME破坏面板&f&f可用于自动破坏其前方的任何方块,并将方块掉落的任何物品直接返回到ME网络.\\n&7[The ME Annihilation Plane can be used to automatically break any blocks in front of it and return anything dropped by the block directly to the ME network. ]&f"
		""
		"作为额外的好处,破坏面板可以像普通挖掘工具一样附魔,以相同的方式影响方块掉落.例如,当附有&e时运&f时,它非常适合处理矿石方块.\\n&7[As an added bonus, the Annihilation Plane can be enchanted in the same way as a regular digging tool, affecting block drops in the same way as that enchanted tool would. This makes it ideal for processing ore blocks when enchanted with Fortune, for example. ]&f"
		"任何添加的附魔都会显著增加面板每次&a破坏&f方块时消耗的能量量.为面板附魔&e效率&f将减少所有其他附魔产生的总体能量消耗,而&e耐久&f附魔则给予面板有时只消耗任何能量的机会,类似于普通工具上的耐久.\\n&7[Any added enchantments significantly increase the amount of energy used by the plane every time a block is broken. Enchanting the plane with Efficiency will decrease the overall energy use incurred by all other enchantments, while the Unbreaking enchantment gives the plane the chance to only use any energy sometimes, similarly to Unbreaking on regular tools.]&f"
	]
	quest.140DE53DC0FCD9F4.quest_subtitle: "进去&7[GET IN]&f"
	quest.15564C11744D6AA0.quest_desc: ["一旦你获得了一套完整的所需&e压印模板&r,就可以开始制作一些&e处理器&f了.这些是制作绝大多数ME连接设备的重要合成材料.\\n&7[Once you have obtained a full set of the required Inscriber Presses, it's time to start making some Processors. These are an important crafting ingredient used to make the large majority of ME-connected devices.]&f"]
	quest.15564C11744D6AA0.title: "处理器&7[Processors]&f"
	quest.16299B9AE87257DC.quest_desc: ["&b无线终端&f的功能与常规终端相同,但是无线的.\\n\\n在它可用于访问网络之前,必须首先通过将其放入&e无线访问点&r的右上角插槽来&e链接&f到网络.如果它没有链接到网络,或者超出范围或电量不足,终端将无法工作.\\n\\n无线终端也可以用&e&a能量卡&f&f升级以提供更大的内部电池.\\n&7[The Wireless Terminal functions identically to a regular terminal, but wirelessly.\\n\\nBefore it can be used to access a network, it must first be linked to the network by placing it into the top-right slot of the Wireless Access Point. If it is not linked to a network, or is out of either range or power, the terminal will not function.\\n\\nWireless terminals can also be upgraded with Energy Cards to provide a larger internal battery.]&f"]
	quest.16299B9AE87257DC.quest_subtitle: "这就是你来这里的目的&7[This is what you're here for]&f"
	quest.16299B9AE87257DC.title: "无线终端&7[Wireless Terminals]&f"
	quest.1710B3D05215A71E.quest_desc: [
		"&bP2P&f(点对点)是AE2中的一个强大系统,允许传输物品、流体甚至更多,无需任何中间ME存储.\\n&7[P2P (peer-to-peer) is a powerful system within AE2, allowing for the transfer of items, fluids and even more without the need for any intermediary ME storage. ]&f"
		""
		"用特定物品右击P2P通道将&e调谐&f该通道,使其能够传输其他东西,例如通过管道的物品、通过线缆的能量、红石信号以及(默认情况下)甚至ME连接本身.\\n&7[Right-clicking on a P2P tunnel with certain items will attune the tunnel into one capable of transferring something else, such as items through pipes, energy through cables, redstone signals and (by default) even ME connections themselves. ]&f"
		""
		"P2P通道必须使用&e&a内存卡&f&f相互链接,详情见下一个任务.\\n&7[P2P tunnels must be linked to one another with the use of a Memory Card, detailed in the next quest.]&f"
	]
	quest.1710B3D05215A71E.quest_subtitle: "去掉中间商&7[Cut out the middleman]&f"
	quest.1710B3D05215A71E.title: "&aP2P通道&f&7[P2P Tunnels]&f"
	quest.18DFB25DC48D8BF7.quest_desc: [
		"The Spatial Containment Structure (SCS) consists of a cage of Spatial Pylons covering the volume you wish to enclose in a Spatial IO cell. At the absolute minimum, an SCS requires three lines of spatial pylon blocks, one for each dimension of the space being contained (length, width, height). "
		""
		"然而,空间IO是一个极其耗电的功能,尤其是在尝试捕获更大空间(最大128x128x128)时.在所需体积周围包含更多的空间塔将提高其整体&e效率&f,使其使用更少的能量来捕获.\\n&7[However, Spatial IO is an extremely power-hungry feature, especially when trying to capture much larger spaces (up to 128x128x128). Having more spatial pylons included in the SCS around the desired volume will increase its overall efficiency, allowing it to use less energy to capture. ]&f"
		""
		"另外,请注意每个单独的塔(无论其长度)占用一个频道.对于特别大的空间,你可能希望构建一个带有控制器的专用网络来容纳所有必需的塔.\\n&7[Also, be mindful that each individual pylon (regardless of its length) takes up one channel. For particularly large spaces, you may wish to build a dedicated network with a controller to fit all the required pylons.]&f"
	]
	quest.1AAF0B31B47AF23D.quest_desc: ["单个ME设备也可以配置为响应红石信号.当用&b&a红石卡&f&f升级后,设备可以配置为仅在红石供能时工作,或者根据需要工作.\\n\\n这种行为也可以应用于ME网络的整个&o部分&r,通过使用&bME切换总线&f.这允许总线另一侧的网络部分仅在总线被红石供能时上线,或者如果使用&e反相&f切换总线则下线.\\n&7[Individual ME devices can also be configured to respond to redstone signals. When upgraded with a Redstone Card, a device can be configured to do work only when powered with redstone or otherwise as needed.\\n\\nThis behavior can also apply to entire sections of an ME network by using an ME Toggle Bus. This allows a section of the network on the other side of the bus to come online only when the bus is powered by redstone, or to go offline if using an inverted toggle bus.]&f"]
	quest.1AAF0B31B47AF23D.title: "红石控制ME&7[Redstone-Controlled ME]&f"
	quest.1B686954D34A0F23.quest_desc: ["&b石英扳手&f的功能与任何常规科技模组的扳手相同.它可以在你右击的面上旋转方块和设备,并在潜行时右击以将其拆除.\\n\\n此扳手有&a赛特斯石英&f和&a下界石英&f两种变体.\\n&7[The Quartz Wrench does what any regular tech mod wrench would do. It rotates blocks and devices along the face you right-click on and dismantles them when right-clicked while sneaking.\\n\\nThis Wrench comes in both Certus Quartz and Nether Quartz varieties.]&f"]
	quest.1B686954D34A0F23.quest_subtitle: "功能完全符合你的预期&7[Does exactly what you'd expect]&f"
	quest.1B686954D34A0F23.title: "石英扳手&7[Quartz Wrench]&f"
	quest.1F7DFA5AA65F2812.quest_desc: ["&b&a加速卡&f&f会根据所升级的设备,提高设备的运行速度或使其能够一次性执行更多操作.\\n\\n对于&e&a分子装配室&f&f,完整的一套5张卡可以将MA完成一次合成所需的时间从一秒(无卡)减少到一&o游戏刻&r.\\n&7[The Acceleration Card, depending on the device being upgraded with it, will either increase the speed at which the device operates or allow the device to carry out more operations in one go.\\n\\nIn the case of the Molecular Assembler, a full set of 5 cards reduces the time taken for the MA to fulfil a craft from one second (with no cards) to one tick.]&f"]
	quest.2077D64428E9C067.quest_desc: [
		"AE2中的一个重要概念是一种称为”&e子网络&f”的技术,其中一个额外的独立ME网络(一个&e子网络&f)与主网络协同工作,以执行某些特定的功能或流程.\\n&7[An important concept within AE2 is a technique known as 'subnetting', wherein an extra separate ME network (a subnetwork) acts in conjunction with the main network to perform some specialised function or process. ]&f"
		""
		"子网络与完全独立的网络之间的区别通常在于使用了&b&a石英纤维&f&f作为线缆部件.当放置在两段原本不连接的线缆之间时,&a石英纤维&f不会在两者之间传输任何数据或频道,而只传输能量.\\n&7[What separates a subnetwork from a completely detached separate network is usually the use of the Quartz Fiber as a cable part. When placed between two otherwise unconnected lengths of cable, the Quartz Fiber transfers no data or channels between the two whatsoever, instead only transmitting power. ]&f"
		""
		"因此,纤维另一端的子网络可以完全由主网络的能源供电,而无需任何额外的专用发电设备.\\n&7[Thus, a subnetwork on the other side of the Fiber can be powered wholly by the main network's power source, without requiring any extra dedicated powergen.]&f"
	]
	quest.2077D64428E9C067.quest_subtitle: "这在合成线缆之外也有用途.&7[This has a use outside of crafting cables.]&f"
	quest.2077D64428E9C067.title: "忘了提&7[Forgot to Mention]&f"
	quest.219932CB19258C16.quest_desc: ["第三级存储元件,提供&e16384&f字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The third tier of storage component, providing 16384 bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.219932CB19258C16.quest_subtitle: "x4^2&7[x4^2]&f"
	quest.219932CB19258C16.title: "16k存储元件&7[16k Storage Component]&f"
	quest.22C4318523A43B49.quest_desc: ["&e终端&f提供了对ME网络任何内容的访问权限.标准的&e&aME终端&f&f只是将网络中的所有内容列为一个大型网格,供你从中取出和放入物品,类似于单个物品栏.\\n\\n&eME合成终端&f是&aME终端&f的扩展,它还提供了一个内置的合成网格,允许使用终端屏幕上可见的网络中包含的任何物品进行便捷的合成.\\n&7[Terminals provide access to any of the contents of an ME network. The standard ME Terminal simply lists everything in the network as one large grid to pull from and insert into, akin to a single inventory.\\n\\nThe ME Crafting Terminal is an extension of the ME Terminal which also provides a built-in crafting grid, allowing for convenient crafting using any item contained in the network and visible through the terminal screen.]&f"]
	quest.22C4318523A43B49.quest_subtitle: "[此处插入Linux用户笑话]&7[[Linux user joke goes here]]&f"
	quest.22C4318523A43B49.title: "终端&7[Terminals]&f"
	quest.234DC1702333EB18.quest_desc: ["&dAEInfinityBooster&f附加模组提供了两种定制的无线增强器,允许无限的连接范围,并可选支持跨维度.\\n&7[The AEInfinityBooster add-on provides two bespoke wireless boosters allowing for infinite connectivity range, with optional cross-dimensional support.]&f"]
	quest.234DC1702333EB18.quest_subtitle: "我不会写《玩具总动员》的台词&7[I'm not writing the Toy Story line]&f"
	quest.234DC1702333EB18.title: "无限增强器&7[Infinity Booster]&f"
	quest.25DBA00422301EDC.quest_desc: ["&a秒&f MEGA级存储元件,提供&e4194304&f(4096k)字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The second MEGA tier of storage component, providing 4194304 (4096k) bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.25DBA00422301EDC.quest_subtitle: "x4&7[x4]&f"
	quest.25DBA00422301EDC.title: "4M存储元件&7[4M Storage Component]&f"
	quest.2893F483C10293E6.quest_desc: [
		"&l欢迎来到&b&d应用能源2&f&f!\\n\\n&d应用能源2&f(简称&oAE2&r)是一个功能极其丰富的&b数字存储&f模组,它允许进行极其高效的存储和各种自动化操作,从而极大地增强你的模组Minecraft体验,从你想要的早期阶段一直到最终阶段.\\n\\n有关本章节之外的AE2更多信息,请查阅维基:\\n&7[lWelcome to Applied Energistics 2!\\n\\nApplied Energistics 2 (or AE2 for short) is an incredibly versatile digital storage mod, allowing for extremely efficient storage and all sorts of automation capabilities to greatly augment your modded Minecraft experience from as early as you want to the very endgame.\\n\\nFor more information on AE2 beyond this chapter, consult the wiki over at]&f"
		"&o&bappliedenergistics.github.io&f&r.\\n&7[appliedenergistics.github.io.]&f"
	]
	quest.2893F483C10293E6.quest_subtitle: "虚拟存储系统&7[Virtual Storage System]&f"
	quest.2893F483C10293E6.title: "&d应用能源2&f&7[Applied Energistics 2]&f"
	quest.2B31E6C1707D8195.quest_desc: ["下一个需要制作的、用于实现无线网络访问的设备是&bME无线访问点&f.&a访问&f点用于通过网络向&e无线终端&f开放无线访问,其具有设定的(有限的)范围,具体取决于访问点中插入了多少个&b无线增强器&f.\\n&7[The next thing to make to allow for wireless network access is the ME Wireless Access Point. The Access Point is used to open the network to wireless access via a wireless terminal, and has a set (finite) range depending on how many Wireless Boosters are inserted into the access point.]&f"]
	quest.2C04B3BA507D5673.quest_desc: ["&b样板&f用于保存由样板供应器执行的编码配方.要将配方编码到样板上,必须使用&bME样板编码终端&f.\\n\\n样板可以设置为保存常规的&e合成&f配方(这需要在其供应器的面上使用&e&a分子装配室&f&f),或者更通用的”&e处理&f”配方,其中任何输入物品都可以由供应器发送到其他机器方块或专门的处理设施中.\\n&7[Patterns are what hold an encoded recipe to be fulfilled by a Pattern Provider. To encode a recipe onto a Pattern, the ME Pattern Encoding Terminal must be used.\\n\\nPatterns can be set to hold either a regular crafting recipe, which will require the use of a Molecular Assembler on the face of its Provider, or a more general 'processing' recipe, wherein any input items can be sent out by the provider into some other machine block or specialised processing plant.]&f"]
	quest.2C04B3BA507D5673.title: "样板&7[Patterns]&f"
	quest.2F16B6A173525277.quest_desc: [
		"对于任何大型ME网络来说,最后一块拼图是&b&aME控制器&f&f.\\n&7[The last piece of the puzzle for any large ME network is the ME Controller. ]&f"
		""
		"控制器为ME网络提供的频道数量远多于临时网络标准的8个频道,其每个面提供32个频道,总计216个频道.\\n&7[A controller supplies an ME Network with a far larger number of channels than the standard 8 channels for ad-hoc networks, providing 32 channels out of each face of the block for a total of 216 channels. ]&f"
		""
		"然而,这仅适用于单方块控制器,因为&aME控制器&f实际上是一个多方块结构.控制器最大可达7x7x7方块大小,并且可以在该最大尺寸内以任何自由形式排列.只要没有任何单个控制器方块在同一平面上被其他4个方块包围,每个单独的方块就可以提供自己独立的一组频道.\\n&7[That's only for a single-block controller, however, since the ME Controller is in fact a multi-block structure. The controller can be up to 7x7x7 blocks in size and can come in any freeform arrangement within that maximum size. Each individual block can then provide its own separate set of channels, so long as no single controller block is surrounded by 4 other blocks along the same plane. ]&f"
		""
		"一个ME网络在任何给定时间只能包含一个多方块控制器.尝试在网络的不同部分连接多个控制器将导致冲突,并使整个网络关闭.\\n&7[An ME Network may only contain one multiblock controller at any given time. Attempting to connect more than one controller on separate parts of the network will cause a conflict, shutting down the whole network.]&f"
	]
	quest.2F556E7919582D2D.quest_desc: ["&b&a元件工作台&f&f允许对存储单元进行”分区”以容纳特定物品,即设置白名单过滤器.它还允许使用某些升级卡(如&a反相卡&f)来升级存储单元,该卡会将上述白名单改为黑名单.\\n\\n通过工作台,还可以为存储单元设置更高或更低的”优先级\\n&7[The Cell Workbench allows for cells to be 'partitioned' to hold specific items, i.e. given a whitelist filter. It also allows the cell to be upgraded with certain upgrade cards such as the Inverter Card, which sets the aforementioned whitelist to be a blacklist instead.\\n\\nCells can also be given a higher or lower 'priority' via the workbench, i.e. allow the cell to be the first to receive certain items until full, or made to wait for other higher-priority cells to fill up first.]&f"]
	quest.2FB231069D2E4E77.quest_desc: ["每个单独的存储单元都有一定的容量,这取决于合成该存储单元时使用的&e元件&f.\\n\\n第一个元件是&b&a1k-ME存储组件&f&f,为给定的存储单元提供&e1024&f”字节”的存储空间.稍后会详细介绍.\\n&7[Each individual cell has a certain capacity dictated by the component that the cell has been crafted with.\\n\\nThe first of the components is the 1k ME Storage Component, providing 1024 'bytes' of storage for a given cell. More on that later.]&f"]
	quest.2FB231069D2E4E77.quest_subtitle: "第一个千字节.&7[The first kilobyte.]&f"
	quest.2FB231069D2E4E77.title: "创建你的第一个&a存储单元&f&7[Creating your first Storage Cell]&f"
	quest.30E853CE699E669B.quest_desc: ["在执行自动合成任务之前,你需要一个设备来实际存储请求本身以及多步骤合成所需的任何中间物品.这个设备被称为&e合成CPU&f.\\n\\n合成CPU是一个多方块结构,需要至少一个&b合成存储&f方块,并可选择性地与其他任何合成单元组合.该多方块结构可以做成任何大小,但必须是一个实心长方体才能形成并相应运作.\\n&7[Before you can carry out an auto-crafting job, you need a device to actually store the request itself along with any interim items for multi-step crafts. This device is known as a crafting CPU.\\n\\nA crafting CPU is a multiblock structure requiring at least one Crafting Storage block, optionally along with any other Crafting Unit. The multiblock can be made in any size, but must be a solid cuboid in order to form and function accordingly.]&f"]
	quest.30E853CE699E669B.quest_subtitle: "下载更多内存&7[Download more RAM]&f"
	quest.3195A7AA874163CD.quest_desc: ["&b均分卡&f是存储单元的一种升级卡,它会预先分配一定数量的物品,这些物品可以被任何单一类型占用.\\n\\n这种行为类似于功能性存储抽屉,其中每个隔间都持有固定数量的物品堆,而不是允许一个隔间的物品溢出到其他隔间并挤占其他种类的物品.\\n&7[The Equal Distribution Card is an upgrade for storage cells that pre-allocates a certain amount of items that can be taken up by any individual type.\\n\\nThis behaviour is comparable to something like a Functional Storage drawer, wherein each compartment holds a set number of stacks as opposed to allowing items from one compartment to leak into the others and crowd other kinds of items out.]&f"]
	quest.3195A7AA874163CD.quest_subtitle: "ME存储&m单元&r抽屉&7[ME Storage Cells Drawers]&f"
	quest.33ADE41526C39AFD.quest_desc: ["这种行为类似于功能性存储抽屉,其中每个隔间都持有固定数量的物品堆,而不是允许一个隔间的物品溢出到其他隔间并挤占其他种类的物品.\\n&7[This behaviour is comparable to something like a Functional Storage drawer, wherein each compartment holds a set number of stacks as opposed to allowing items from one compartment to leak into the others and crowd other kinds of items out.]&f"]
	quest.361CCBD353D6FF34.quest_desc: [
		"有了1k存储元件,你现在可以为自己合成一个1k ME物品&a存储单元&f,以启动你的数字物品存储系统.你很可能希望你的大部分存储空间用于物品,所以你可能会想制作几个&bME物品&a存储单元&f&f.\\n&7[With the 1k Storage Component, you can now craft yourself a 1k ME Item Storage Cell to start your digital item storage system. You'll most likely want the majority of your storage to be for items, so you'll probably want to make a few ME Item Storage Cells. ]&f"
		""
		"每个ME物品&a存储单元&f最多可以容纳63种不同类型的物品.添加到存储单元中的每种新类型的物品都会占用存储单元总容量(以字节计)的一定比例.对于已存在的&a循环检测&f类型,1”字节”对应8个相同类型的物品.\\n&7[ME Item Storage Cells can each hold up to 63 different types of items. Each new type of item added to a cell will take up a certain fraction of the storage cell's total capacity in bytes. For each type already present, 1 'byte' counts for 8 items of that same type. ]&f"
		""
		"例如,一个只装有圆石的1k物品&a存储单元&f最多可以容纳8128个圆石(8*1024b - 8b/类型 * 1类型).\\n&7[As an example, a 1k Item Storage Cell containing only cobblestone can hold up to 8128 cobblestone (8*1024b - 8b/type * 1 type). ]&f"
		""
		"如果存储单元是空的,可以通过将其拆解为相应的元件和外壳来重新利用.操作方法是手持存储单元,潜行并在空中右击.\\n&7[If a cell is empty, it can be repurposed by disassembling it into its respective component and housing. This is done by sneaking and right-clicking in the air with the cell in your hand.]&f"
	]
	quest.361CCBD353D6FF34.title: "物品存储&7[Item Storage]&f"
	quest.371A382CF1DDF2B2.quest_desc: ["&b&a容量卡&f&f允许升级后的总线携带更大的过滤器.升级了容量卡的导入和导出总线可以从仅支持一个过滤物品增加到最多九个槽位的过滤器,而存储总线将从18个槽位增加到最多63个.\\n&7[The Capacity Card allows a bus upgraded with it to carry a larger filter. Import and Export buses upgraded with capacity cards can go from supporting only one filtered item each to their maximum nine-slot filter, while Storage buses will go from 18 slots to a maximum of 63.]&f"]
	quest.3B42CCC19D23EC6D.quest_desc: ["&a秒&f级存储元件,提供&e4096&f字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The second tier of storage component, providing 4096 bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.3B42CCC19D23EC6D.quest_subtitle: "x4&7[x4]&f"
	quest.3B42CCC19D23EC6D.title: "4k存储元件&7[4k Storage Component]&f"
	quest.3CE3D9245F8EC005.quest_desc: ["第四级MEGA存储元件,提供&e67108864&f(65536k)字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The fourth MEGA tier of storage component, providing 67108864 (65536k) bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.3CE3D9245F8EC005.quest_subtitle: "x4^3&7[x4^3]&f"
	quest.3CE3D9245F8EC005.title: "64M存储元件&7[64M Storage Component]&f"
	quest.3DDB0DDA7571B2C1.quest_desc: ["&b&aME标准发信器&f&f在配置为响应特定物品及其数量时,会根据网络中存储的该物品数量是低于、高于还是等于给定数量而发出红石信号.\\n\\n例如,这可以用于在某种资源低于给定的最小数量时,自动用红石信号开启某些机器以自动合成该资源.\\n&7[The ME Level Emitter, when configured with a specific item and quantity of it to respond to, will emit a redstone signal depending on whether that item stored in the network either falls below, goes above or equals the given quantity.\\n\\nThis can be used, for example, to automatically switch certain machines on with redstone to auto-craft a resource when it falls below a given minimum amount.]&f"]
	quest.3DDB0DDA7571B2C1.title: "&aME标准发信器&f&7[ME Level Emitter]&f"
	quest.3E3DF8E967D95DB0.quest_desc: ["当使用64k或更高级别的存储元件时,&a物质聚合器&f能够凝聚显著更多的物品来产生一个&b奇点&f.单个奇点需要湮灭256000个物品.这正好是&o4000组&r!\\n\\n看看当你将这个奇点与一块&e&a末影尘&f&f一起扔在地上时会发生什么.在这个过程中你将不得不对周围环境造成一些破坏,但幸运的是AE2提供了自己的&b微型TNT&f来最小化这种破坏.\\n&7[When using a 64k storage component or higher, the Matter Condenser becomes able to condense significantly more to produce a Singularity. A single singularity requires 256000 items to be voided. That's exactly 4000 stacks!\\n\\nSee what happens when you throw this singularity on the ground with a piece of Ender Dust. You'll have to deal some damage to the surroundings while you're at it, but thankfully AE2 offers its own Tiny TNT to minimise that.]&f"]
	quest.3E3DF8E967D95DB0.quest_subtitle: "超凝聚物质&7[Hyper-Condensed Matter]&f"
	quest.3E3DF8E967D95DB0.title: "超凝聚物质&7[Hyper-Condensed Matter]&f"
	quest.4597D3B3BDC2BED5.quest_desc: ["&b&a分子装配室&f&f是AE2中相当于自动工作台的设备,需要它来完成任何和所有的&e合成&f样板任务.\\n\\n&a分子装配室&f能够向与其连接的其他ME设备传输能量和频道,但其本身不会占用频道.最多可以有6个MA连接到一个样板供应器(如果使用的话),以允许并行执行更多合成.\\n\\n每个MA也有自己专用的单个合成样板槽位,使其在供能时可以独立运作.以这种方式操作时,任何插入MA的匹配物品将自动合成为样板的结果.\\n&7[The Molecular Assembler is AE2's equivalent of an automatic crafting table, required to fulfil any and all crafting pattern jobs.\\n\\nMolecular Assemblers are capable of transferring power and channels to other ME devices connected to it, but will not themselves take up a channel. Up to 6 MAs can be connected to a single Pattern Provider (if employed) to allow for more crafts to be done in parallel.\\n\\nMAs also each have their own dedicated slot for a single crafting pattern, allowing them to function standalone when powered. When operated in this way, any matching items inserted into the MA will be automatically crafted into the result of the pattern.]&f"]
	quest.460A8F17F3ED6CAF.quest_desc: ["在任何大型模组包的游玩过程中,都会遇到这样一个时刻:即使是最高标准等级的存储单元也无法满足你可能积累的物品和资源数量.\\n\\n这就是&d&aMEGA存储单元&f&f附加模组发挥作用的地方,它将可用的存储等级扩展到了兆字节领域.这些新等级中的第一个由&b&a1M-MEGA存储组件&f&f提供,提供1024&o千&r字节,即&e1048576&f字节的存储空间.\\n&7[There comes a point in any playthrough of a large modpack where even the highest standard tier of storage cell doesn't cut it for the amount of items and resources that you may be accumulating.\\n\\nThis is where the MEGA Cells add-on comes in, extending the available tiers of storage into the megabyte territory. The first of these new tiers is given by the 1M MEGA Storage Component, providing 1024 kilobytes, or 1048576 bytes, of storage.]&f"]
	quest.460A8F17F3ED6CAF.quest_subtitle: "第一个兆字节.&7[The first MEGAbyte.]&f"
	quest.460A8F17F3ED6CAF.title: "1M存储元件&7[1M Storage Component]&f"
	quest.4B76FE0348DB0E45.quest_desc: ["&a量子桥卡&f是另一种实现跨维度无线访问应用能源系统的方法.你需要在基地连接一个量子桥,并在你的终端中放入一张&a量子桥卡&f.然后,这些通道通过一个&a量子缠绕态奇点&f绑定在一起,以便无论你走到哪里都能访问.\\n&7[The Quantum Bridge Card is an alternate method to get wireless interdimensional access to your Applied Energistics system. You will need a Quantum Bridge connected at your base and a Quantum Bridge Card in your terminal. These tunnels are then bound together with a Quantum Entangled Singularity to gain access wherever you go.]&f"]
	quest.4BF0BB763BFFACF0.quest_desc: [
		"接下来你可能需要的最重要的资源是&e福鲁伊克斯&f,它用于绝大多数AE2设备,并且是合成ME网络中所有线缆的基础.\\n&7[Arguably the most important resource you will need next is Fluix, used throughout the vast majority of AE2 devices and serving as a base for crafting all of the cabling within an ME network. ]&f"
		""
		"你通常需要大规模生产这些,方法是制作&b&a福鲁伊克斯水晶&f&f,将&e&a下界石英&f&f、&e&o充能&r&e &a赛特斯石英&f&r和&e红石&f一起扔进一池水中.这将给你一个&e&a福鲁伊克斯水晶&f&r,你可以在压印器中将其磨成粉.\\n&7[You'll typically want to mass produce these, and the way to do so is to make a Fluix Crystal by throwing Nether Quartz, Charged Certus quartz and Redstone together in a pool of water. This will give you a Fluix Crystal which you can turn to dust in an Inscriber.]&f"
	]
	quest.4BF0BB763BFFACF0.title: "福鲁伊克斯&7[Fluix]&f"
	quest.4E8A05C3BFA80540.quest_desc: ["可以说,&d应用能源2&f最重要的方面是其存储系统,它利用了数字&e&a存储单元&f&f.这些单元可以通过&e&aME箱子&f&r(用于单个单元)或&e&aME驱动器&f&r(用于多个单元)进行访问.\\n\\n&b&aME箱子&f&f一次可容纳一个存储单元,然后可以通过同一网络上的任何其他终端进行读取和写入.&aME箱子&f本身也在顶部提供了自己的终端屏幕,但仅能访问其包含的单元.\\n\\n&b&aME驱动器&f&f可以在单个方块和单个ME通道的空间内容纳多达10个不同类型的&a存储单元&f.但是,它不提供自己的终端屏幕,需要网络上的某个外部终端来访问存储.\\n&7[Arguably the most important aspect of Applied Energistics 2 is its storage system, making use of digital Storage Cells. These cells are accessible through either an ME Chest for single cells, or an ME Drive for multiple cells.\\n\\nThe ME Chest holds a single Cell at a time, which can then be read from and written to from any other terminal on the same network. The ME Chest itself also provides its own terminal screen on the top with specific access only to the cell it contains.\\n\\nThe ME Drive can hold up to 10 assorted Storage Cells in the space of a single block and a single ME channel. However, it does not provide its own terminal screen, requiring some external terminal elsewhere on the network for storage access.]&f"]
	quest.4E8A05C3BFA80540.quest_subtitle: "物品即文件系统&7[Items as a file system]&f"
	quest.4E8A05C3BFA80540.title: "&a存储&f&7[The Storage]&f"
	quest.5034A9137E0F3D3D.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下,未经&6AllTheMods Team&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非其发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被有意隐藏,如果你看到此信息,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.51A57E142C686C8F.quest_desc: ["第五个也是最后一个MEGA级存储元件,提供&e268435456&f(262144k)字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The fifth and final MEGA tier of storage component, providing 268435456 (262144k) bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.51A57E142C686C8F.quest_subtitle: "x4^4&7[x4^4]&f"
	quest.51A57E142C686C8F.title: "256M存储元件&7[256M Storage Component]&f"
	quest.51DE3157DE3E57B8.quest_desc: [
		"存储固然很好,但如果存储系统塞满了需要合成和处理成其他东西的原材料,而你仍然不得不手动操作,那这个存储系统又有什么用呢？\\n&7[Storage is nice and all that, but what good is a storage system if it's clogged up with raw materials needing to be crafted and processed into something and you're still stuck with having to do so manually? ]&f"
		""
		"AE2的&e自动合成&f系统始于&bME样板供应器&f.&a样板&f供应器持有称为&b样板&f的物品(将在下一个任务中介绍),这些样板被编程为包含将输入物品转化为特定输出的配方.一个供应器最多可容纳9个样板.\\n&7[AE2's auto-crafting system begins with the ME Pattern Provider. The Pattern Provider holds certain items called Patterns (covered in the next quest) which are programmed to hold some recipe that turns input items into a certain output. Up to 9 patterns can fit in one provider. ]&f"
		""
		"你通常会使用散布在基地各处的多个样板供应器,这就是为什么拥有一个&b样板&a访问终端&f&f很有用,它可以远程访问你更广泛的ME网络上所有供应器的内容.\\n&7[You'll often be making use of multiple pattern providers scattered all throughout your base, which is why it's useful to have a Pattern Access Terminal to remotely access the contents of any and all providers on your wider ME network.]&f"
	]
	quest.51DE3157DE3E57B8.quest_subtitle: "下达订单&7[Order up]&f"
	quest.51DE3157DE3E57B8.title: "自动合成&7[Auto-Crafting]&f"
	quest.5233A447BAA4593C.quest_desc: ["&bME智能线缆&f和&b致密智能线缆&f在通道分配方面的功能与已介绍的线缆相同,但它们还会沿着自身以彩色线条的形式直观显示正在使用的通道数量.\\n&7[The ME Smart Cable and Dense Smart Cable function identically to the covered cables in terms of channel distribution, but will also visibly display the amount of channels they are using as coloured lines along themselves.]&f"]
	quest.5233A447BAA4593C.quest_subtitle: "'智.能.'&7['S.M.R.T.']&f"
	quest.5233A447BAA4593C.title: "高级布线&7[Advanced Cabling]&f"
	quest.523853C1C4E688BA.quest_desc: ["第四级存储元件,提供&e65536&f字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The fourth tier of storage component, providing 65536 bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.523853C1C4E688BA.quest_subtitle: "x4^3&7[x4^3]&f"
	quest.523853C1C4E688BA.title: "64k存储元件&7[64k Storage Component]&f"
	quest.525F25F4ADE45B50.quest_desc: [
		"&b&aME成型面板&f&f的功能类似于存储总线,但将世界本身视为其存储介质.换句话说,它会将其过滤器中任何方块直接放置在自己前方.\\n&7[The ME Formation Plane acts similarly to the Storage Bus, but treats the world itself as its storage medium. In other words, it will place down any block in its filter directly in front of itself. ]&f"
		""
		"这对于某些方块只需放置并用特定工具破坏即可处理的情况很有用.\\n&7[This can be useful for situations where a block can be processed simply by placing it and breaking it with a certain tool.]&f"
	]
	quest.525F25F4ADE45B50.quest_subtitle: "出去&7[GET OUT]&f"
	quest.55186B8602689B66.quest_desc: [
		"&b&a内存卡&f&f是一种具有两种不同功能的工具.&a较简单&f的功能是保存各种设备的配置(例如白名单过滤器),以便复制到另一个同类设备上.\\n&7[The Memory Card is a tool with two different functions. The simplest of the two is to save various devices' configurations (such as whitelist filters) to be copied over to another device of the same kind. ]&f"
		""
		"内存卡的&a第二个&f功能是将&eP2P通道&f链接在一起.这样做时,被链接的P2P通道将被分配一个唯一的ID,该ID存储在内存卡上以供进一步链接.\\n&7[The second function of a memory card is to link P2P tunnels together. When doing so, the P2P tunnel being linked will be assigned a unique ID, which is stored on the memory card for further linking.]&f"
	]
	quest.5AA3E5DFECB4AC4D.quest_desc: ["自然地,AE2提供了自己的方式来显著加速晶体生长.\\n\\n将这些放置在萌芽水晶周围,为它们提供一些能量,然后看着你的水晶生长!\\n&7[Naturally, AE2 provides its own way to dramatically speed up crystal growth.\\n\\nPlace these around your Budding Crystals, give them some power, and watch your crystals grow!]&f"]
	quest.5BB887411B8B38FA.quest_desc: ["至于无线扩展ME网络本身,第一步确实有些非正统.\\n\\n&b&a物质聚合器&f&f是AE2的垃圾桶,可以销毁放入其中的任何物品.然而,当安装&e存储元件&f时,聚合器可以利用被销毁物品残留的一些能量并将其存储起来,用足够的浓缩能量制造两种特殊的合成物品.\\n\\n这两种物品中的第一种是&b&a物质球&f&f,至少需要1k存储元件和相当于256个物品的被销毁材料.\\n&7[As for wirelessly expanding the ME Network itself, the first step is admittedly somewhat unorthodox.\\n\\nThe Matter Condenser is AE2's take on a trash can, voiding any items inserted into it. When fitted with a Storage Component, however, the condenser can harness some left-over energy from the item being voided and store it to make two special crafting items out of enough concentrated energy.\\n\\nThe first of these two items is the Matter Ball, requiring at least a 1k storage component and 256 items' worth of voided material.]&f"]
	quest.5BB887411B8B38FA.title: "凝聚物质&7[Condensed Matter]&f"
	quest.5C22E3103544B120.quest_desc: ["To connect the vast majority of your ME network together, you will need some cable. ME Glass Cable is the first and most basic kind of cable, and you'll be making this all throughout as the first step towards crafting the other kinds of cable.\\n\\nBoth glass cables and their covered counterpart can carry up to 8 channels along a single section of cabling. Unlike glass cables, covered cables can subsequently be crafted into dense covered cables, capable of carrying up to 32 channels. However, most 'multipart' devices such as buses and terminals cannot be directly attached to dense cables, requiring normal-width cables to form a connection instead.\\n\\nAll cables can also be crafted with dye to colour them. Uncoloured ('Fluix') cables can connect to any other colour of cable, but otherwise differently-coloured cables will never connect to one another."]
	quest.5C22E3103544B120.title: "基础布线&7[Basic Cabling]&f"
	quest.5CD8D169181C7339.quest_desc: ["最后这三件物品或多或少是AE2提供的一些额外玩具,不一定完全符合这些任务树的分类.\\n\\n&b充能手杖&f只是一个简单的充能手杖,每次攻击造成3颗心的伤害并消耗300AE.它还使用1.9版本之前的战斗机制,这意味着你可以像过去的美好时光一样连续点击使用它.\\n\\n&b&a熵变机械臂&f&f,当&o使用&r于世界中的某些方块时,会就地烧炼它们,例如将沙子烧成玻璃,将金属矿石烧成金属锭.否则,它只会在方块上点火.\\n\\n最后,&b&a物质炮&f&f的功能类似于&a染色器&f,作为一个专门用于容纳'弹药'物品(如&a物质球&f和铁/金粒)的单元,然后可以发射出去对生物造成伤害或破坏方块.在&a物质炮&f中,较重的'弹药'&a物质球&f可以用&b&a染色球&f&f替代,这会在被射击的方块表面施加油漆飞溅效果.&b流明&a染色球&f&f是&a物质炮&f专用的染色球变体,其油漆飞溅效果一旦存在于世界中也会发出一些光.\\n&7[These last three items are more or less some extra toys provided by AE2 and don't necessarily fit under any of these quest trees.\\n\\nThe Charged Staff is just a simple powered staff which deals 3 hearts of damage and consumes 300AE per hit. It also uses pre-1.9 combat mechanics, meaning that you can spam-click with this like in the good old days.\\n\\nThe Entropy Manipulator, when used on certain blocks in the world, will smelt them in-place, such as sand to glass and metal ores to metal ingots. If not, it will simply light a fire on the block.\\n\\nFinally, the Matter Cannon functions similarly to the Color Applicator as a dedicated cell for holding 'ammo' items such as Matter Balls and iron/gold nuggets, which can then be fired out to deal damage to mobs or break blocks. Heavier 'ammo'Matter Balls in a Matter Cannon can be substituted with Paint Balls, which will apply a paint splatter effect on the face of whatever block being fired at. Lumen Paint Balls are a variant of paint balls exclusively used by the Matter Cannon, whose paint splatters also give off some light once present in the world.]&f"]
	quest.5CD8D169181C7339.quest_subtitle: "&a温度过高&f,不适合ATF&7[Too hot for the ATF]&f"
	quest.5CD8D169181C7339.title: "这...是武器？&7[The... Weapons?]&f"
	quest.5E24012A3D9B72A1.quest_desc: [
		"物品并不是唯一可以存储在ME单元中的东西.&bME流体&a存储单元&f&f可以存储液体,例如水、熔岩以及各种模组添加的油和燃料,这里仅举几例.\\n&7[Items are not the only things that can be stored in ME cells. ME Fluid Storage Cells can store liquids such as water, lava and any variety of modded oils and fuels, just to give a few examples. ]&f"
		""
		"请注意,所有存储单元,无论设计用于存储什么,仅在外壳上有所不同；物品单元和流体单元都使用相同类型的存储元件制造.\\n&7[Note that all storage cells, regardless of what they're designed to store, only differ in terms of their housing; both item and fluid cells use the same kind of storage component to make. ]&f"
		""
		"对于流体,1字节等于8桶(8000mb).\\n&7[For fluids, 1 byte equals 8 buckets (8000mb).]&f"
	]
	quest.5E6585F7627247E3.quest_desc: ["当作为升级应用于任何支持的设备(如接口或输出总线)时,&b合成卡&f允许该设备自动为其所需的(过滤)物品发出自己的合成请求.可以设置合成CPU仅响应这些请求,以防止占用用于玩家请求合成的CPU.\\n\\n当&e等级发射器&f用合成卡升级后,可以配置其发出红石信号以直接促进合成,通过在其给定物品的合成任务被检测到时&o发出&r信号,或专门&o为了&r合成该物品而发出信号.后者适用于制造给定物品唯一需要的就是红石信号的情况,甚至不需要合成样板.\\n&7[When applied as an upgrade to any supported device such as an Interface or Export Bus, the Crafting Card allows the device in question to automatically send out its own crafting requests for a required (filtered) item. Crafting CPUs can be set to respond only to these requests to prevent taking up CPUs meant for player-requested crafts.\\n\\nWhen the Level Emitter is upgraded with the Crafting Card, it can be configured to emit redstone in order to directly facilitate in crafting, by emitting a signal either while a crafting job for its given item is detected or specifically to craft the item. The latter would apply for cases where the only thing needed to make a given item is a redstone signal, without even requiring a crafting pattern.]&f"]
	quest.5E6585F7627247E3.quest_subtitle: "自动化,以升级形式呈现!&7[Automation in upgrade form!]&f"
	quest.5E7E35CCAF1C88EE.quest_desc: ["&bME输入总线&f会定期从其面向的任何外部存储中吸取物品.可以选择性地设置过滤器,使其仅从所述容器中提取特定物品.\\n&7[The ME Import Bus periodically sucks items in from whatever external storage the bus is facing. It can optionally be filtered to only take in certain items from said inventory.]&f"]
	quest.5E7E35CCAF1C88EE.quest_subtitle: "输入&7[The I]&f"
	quest.5F56892CD904C40F.quest_desc: ["第五个也是最后一个AE2标准级存储元件,提供&e262144&f字节的存储空间.\\n&7[The fifth and final AE2-standard tier of storage component, providing 262144 bytes of storage.]&f"]
	quest.5F56892CD904C40F.quest_subtitle: "x4^4&7[x4^4]&f"
	quest.5F56892CD904C40F.title: "256k存储元件&7[256k Storage Component]&f"
	quest.6144202A97C6CD1C.quest_desc: ["&b&a石英切割刀&f&f,就像扳手一样,有下界石英和赛特斯石英两种版本,是一种有用的随身携带的合成工具.\\n\\n线缆也可以通过在其间连接&b线缆锚&f来分离,而无需染色,线缆锚使用此刀合成,同一把刀最多可合成50次才会损坏.\\n\\n线缆锚也可用于合成&b线缆伪装板&f,允许你通过用任意方块的表面覆盖线缆来将其隐藏在墙内.虽然伪装板的配方在JEI中隐藏,但你仍然可以通过在合成网格中放置任意普通方块并用4个线缆锚围绕它来合成它们.\\n\\n除了合成锚之外,切割刀还有另一个用途:右键单击刀会打开一个小型GUI,允许你合成&b&a名称压印模板&f&f.当给定一个名称后,这些压印模板可以在压印机内使用,用压印模板的名称重命名任何输入物品.两个这样的压印模板可以在压印机中连接,将物品重命名为顶部压印模板的名称,后跟底部压印模板的名称.\\n&7[The Quartz Cutting Knife, like the wrench, comes in both nether and certus quartz flavours and is a useful crafting tool to have on hand.\\n\\nCables can also be separated without needing to be coloured by attaching a Cable Anchor between them, crafted using this knife and craftable up to 50 times with the same knife before it breaks.\\n\\nCable Anchors can also be used to craft Cable Facades, allowing you to disguise cables within walls by covering them with the face of an arbitrary block. While facade recipes are hidden in JEI, you can still craft them by taking any regular block and surrounding it with 4 cable anchors in the crafting grid.\\n\\nAside from crafting anchors, the cutting knife also has another use: right-clicking with the knife will open a small GUI that allows you to craft Inscriber Name Presses. When given a name, these presses can be used inside of an Inscriber to rename any input item with the name of the press. Two of these presses can be concatenated in the inscriber to rename the item to the name of the top press, followed by the bottom one.]&f"]
	quest.6144202A97C6CD1C.quest_subtitle: "刀下之物&7[Under the knife]&f"
	quest.6144202A97C6CD1C.title: "线缆锚&7[Cable Anchor]&f"
	quest.6431A384DDFBF439.quest_desc: [
		"&b&a网络工具&f&f是整个AE2中的重要工具,用于在屏幕上显示网络的各项详细信息,例如总体能耗和存储情况.\\n&7[The Network Tool is an important tool throughout AE2, which is used to display various details of a network on-screen such as overall power consumption and storage. ]&f"
		""
		"作为额外的好处,它还提供了一个自己的小型物品栏,用于存放&e升级卡&f,当查看任何可升级设备的屏幕时,可以访问此物品栏以便轻松更换.但是,它不能像普通扳手那样旋转连接到ME网络的方块,只能在潜行时拆卸它们.\\n&7[As an added bonus, it also provides its own small inventory used to hold upgrade cards, which can be accessed when looking at any upgradeable device's screen for easy replacement. However, it cannot rotate blocks attached to the ME network like a regular wrench, only dismantle them when sneaking.]&f"
	]
	quest.6431A384DDFBF439.title: "&a网络工具&f&7[Network Tools]&f"
	quest.68B0B3DAF1145191.quest_desc: ["在AE2中起步,你最初需要的两样东西是&b充能器&f和&b压印机&f.\\n\\n&b充能器&f在供能后,会为&e&a赛特斯石英水晶&f&r充能.这些&e充能赛特斯水晶&r随后可用于生产&e福鲁伊克斯&f,这是模组中的另一种重要资源.它也可以用于为任何存储能量的物品充能.\\n\\n&b压印机&f可用于将AE2中的各种石英晶体转化为粉末形式,但更重要的是用于制造特殊的&e印刷电路&f和&e处理器&f,这将在下一个任务中变得更清楚.\\n&7[Two of the very first things you will need to get started in AE2 are the Charger and the Inscriber.\\n\\nThe Charger, when supplied with power, will take Certus Quartz Crystals and charge them. These Charged Certus Crystals can then be used in the production of Fluix, another important resource in the mod. It can also be used to charge any item that stores power.\\n\\nThe Inscriber can be used to turn the various quartz crystals in AE2 into their dust form, but more importantly is used to fabricate special Printed Circuits and Processors, as will become clearer in the next quest.]&f"]
	quest.68B0B3DAF1145191.quest_subtitle: "首要之事&7[First Things First]&f"
	quest.68B0B3DAF1145191.title: "首要之事&7[First Things First]&f"
	quest.69B7DE2283B4EE6C.quest_desc: ["&b&a并行处理单元&f&f通过允许样板供应器更快地向其连接的设备发送物品,或同时工作以制造多个所需成分,来帮助加速合成任务.\\n\\n基础的AE2协处理器提供一个协处理器'线程'来协助此过程,而来自&d&aMEGA存储单元&f&f的协处理单元在一个这样的方块中提供4个线程.\\n&7[The Crafting Co-Processing Unit helps speed up crafting jobs by allowing pattern providers to either send items out to their connected devices faster or to work concurrently to make multiple required ingredients.\\n\\nThe base AE2 co-processor provides one co-processor 'thread' to assist this, while the co-processing unit from MEGA Cells provides 4 threads in a single such block.]&f"]
	quest.69B7DE2283B4EE6C.quest_subtitle: "下载更多CPU核心&7[Download more CPU cores]&f"
	quest.6D54B45CDA70FEAB.quest_desc: ["&b&a能量卡&f&f可以应用于大多数可充电设备,如&a便携元件&f和无线终端(稍后介绍),以增加&o它们的&r能量缓冲.\\n&7[The Energy Card can be applied to most chargeable devices like Portable Cells and Wireless Terminals (covered later) to also increase their energy buffer.]&f"]
	quest.6E15447FC3D678E0.quest_desc: ["&b&a模糊卡&f&f允许过滤的物品无论任何(NBT)元数据(如耐久度或附魔)都能匹配,而&b&a反相卡&f&f则可将此类总线上的过滤器从白名单切换为黑名单.\\n&7[The Fuzzy Card allows a filtered item to be matched regardless of any (NBT) metadata such as damage or enchantments, while the Inverter Card toggles the filter on such buses from being a whitelist to being a blacklist.]&f"]
	quest.6E15447FC3D678E0.quest_subtitle: "剩余的两张输入输出卡&7[The remaining two IO cards]&f"
	quest.6E15447FC3D678E0.title: "大致来说&7[Loosely Speaking]&f"
	quest.6F3D0A248B5A9CA2.quest_desc: [
		"&b空间&a存储单元&f&f用于各自容纳一个定义的体积,有三种不同的容量,最多可容纳2x2x2、16x16x16和128x128x128方块的空间.\\n&7[Spatial Storage Cells are used to hold one defined volume each, and come in three different capacities allowing for a maximum of 2x2x2, 16x16x16 and 128x128x128 blocks' worth of space. ]&f"
		""
		"编码后,一个单元会在空间存储&e维度&f内分配一个空间区域,以及一个对应于分配给该单元区域的唯一ID.编码后的单元仍然可以在&a空间IO端口&f内使用,以检索任何存储的方块和实体.\\n&7[Upon encoding, a cell is allocated a section of space within the spatial storage dimension, along with a unique ID corresponding to the region allocated to the cell. An encoded cell can still be used within the Spatial IO Port to retrieve any stored blocks and entities. ]&f"
		""
		"从此以后,任何位于该存储单元空间区域内,或位于与初始编码所用尺寸相同的SCS(空间压缩存储)中的方块,都可以分别移回主世界或移入空间维度.如果空间区域和SCS内都有方块,它们将相应地进行位置互换.\\n&7[From then on, any blocks contained either within the cell's region of space or in an SCS with the same size as the one used for the initial encoding can be moved back into the overworld or into the spatial dimension respectively. If there are blocks both within the spatial region and within the SCS, these will simply swap places accordingly.]&f"
	]
	quest.6F3D0A248B5A9CA2.title: "空间&a存储单元&f&7[Spatial Storage Cell]&f"
	quest.748EC01C031E661A.quest_desc: [
		"当然,作为一个空岛整合包,情况会略有不同.就像制作无瑕的萌芽方块一样,你也需要以不同的方式制作你的压印模板.\\n&7[Of course, being a skyblock things will function slightly differently. As with the creation of flawless budding blocks, you will also want to create your inscriber presses differently.]&f"
		""
		"在这个整合包中,压印模板直接从压印器中获得.没看到配方？查看下一页,那里有不复制模板,而是制作你第一个模板的配方.\\n&7[In this pack, that is from the inscriber directly. Dont see the recipe? Check the next page for the one that does not duplicate the press, but creates your first.]&f"
	]
	quest.74FC0DDDB91DB172.quest_desc: ["为了让生活更轻松,应用能源2提供了一整套用于操作ME数据的设备,例如在世界范围内移动存储的物品.\\n\\n&b&aME接口&f&f就是这些设备之一.作为输入设备,接口允许任何物品/流体等通过外部管道输入,然后自动存储到该接口所连接的ME网络中.\\n\\n作为输出设备,接口可以配置为从ME网络中保持一定数量的特定物品在其内部库存中可用.这使得物品可以被某些外部来源接收,比如另一个玩家或某种管道.\\n&7[To make life that much easier, AE2 provides a whole suite of devices for the manipulation of ME data, i.e. moving stored items around the world.\\n\\nThe ME Interface is one of these devices. As an input device, the Interface allows any item/fluid/etc to be piped externally through it, which is then automatically stored in the ME Network that the interface is connected to.\\n\\nAs an output device, the Interface can be configured to keep a certain available amount of a stored item in stock, from the ME network to its own internal inventory. This allows items to then be received by some external source like another player or some pipe.]&f"]
	quest.74FC0DDDB91DB172.quest_subtitle: "喂,喂,喂!&7[OI, OI, OI!]&f"
	quest.74FC0DDDB91DB172.title: "输入输出&7[The IO]&f"
	quest.77C9EE701F72586D.quest_desc: [
		"&b&a便携元件&f&f的功能与常规存储元件相同,可以放入箱子或驱动器并相应地进行填充.\\n&7[Portable Cells function identically to regular cells in that they can be inserted into a chest or drive and filled accordingly. ]&f"
		""
		"然而,与常规存储元件不同,其内容也可以通过元件物品本身独立访问,有点像数字化的ME风味背包.\\n&7[However, unlike regular cells, their contents can also be accessed standalone via the cell item itself, a bit like a digital ME-flavoured backpack.]&f"
	]
	quest.78311531069807DE.quest_desc: ["在&d应用能源2&f中,每个ME网络都有一定数量的&e频道&f可用,这简单来说就是整个网络可以容纳多少个联网设备.\\n\\n根据经验法则,任何或多或少直接处理ME数据(网络中存储的物品)并执行某种形式输入/输出的设备都会占用一个频道.通常只涉及网络内部能量存储的组件,如&e&a能量单元&f&f和&e压印器&f,&o不&r占用频道.\\n\\n没有&b&aME控制器&f&f的网络被称为”临时”网络,最多只支持8个频道.\\n&7[In Applied Energistics 2, every ME network has a certain number of channels available, which simply means how many networked devices can fit on the whole network.\\n\\nAs a rule of thumb, any device that more or less handles ME data directly (items stored within the network) and carries out some form of I/O will take up a channel. Usually components that are only concerned with the internal power storage of the network, like Energy Cells and Inscribers, do not take up channels.\\n\\nNetworks without an ME Controller are known as 'ad-hoc' networks and only support a maximum of 8 channels.]&f"]
	quest.7B7D1F0CB326B28F.quest_desc: ["&b&aME-IO端口&f&f允许快速在不同存储介质(如ME存储元件和连接到存储总线的外部容器)之间重新排列ME网络的存储内容.\\n\\n当在左侧的输入槽中放入一个存储元件时,可以切换&aIO端口&f,以将元件清空到其他ME存储中,或者用分散在其他存储中的特定物品填充(理想情况下是经过分区的)元件.\\n&7[The ME IO Port allows for the contents of an ME network's storage to be quickly rearranged between different storage media such as ME cells and external containers connected to storage buses.\\n\\nWhen a cell is inserted in an input slot on the left, the IO Port can be toggled to either empty the cell out into other ME storages or fill the (ideally, partitioned) cell with certain items spread out across other storages.]&f"]
	quest.7B7D1F0CB326B28F.quest_subtitle: "碎片整理&7[Defragmentation]&f"
	quest.7EFBAF3E281D2EBE.quest_desc: [
		"&bME存储总线&f,当面向某个外部存储容器时,将使该容器能够像ME网络的一部分一样被使用,允许纯粹通过ME从容器中取出物品或向其中插入物品.\\n&7[The ME Storage Bus, when facing some external storage container, will allow the container to be used as though it were part of the ME network, allowing items to be taken out from the container or inserted into it purely via ME. ]&f"
		""
		"存储总线可以被过滤并设置特定的优先级,使得特定物品会尝试优先进入所连接的存储,但它不会追溯性地将网络中其他地方的任何过滤物品移动到其连接的存储中.\\n&7[Storage buses can be filtered and given specific priorities such that specific items will try to go to the attached storage first, however it will not retroactively move any filtered items from anywhere else in the network to its attached storage.]&f"
	]
	quest.7EFBAF3E281D2EBE.quest_subtitle: "备用箱子&7[The spare chest]&f"
	task.08DA73B1AC17E5F5.title: "合成存储&7[Crafting Storage]&f"
	task.1076BC82EECB73F5.title: "石英扳手&7[Quartz Wrenches]&f"
	task.14DEFFB80CC96BC1.title: "ME致密包覆线缆&7[ME Dense Covered Cables]&f"
	task.23D186249A999B8C.title: "石英切割刀&7[Quartz Cutting Knives]&f"
	task.338A6DA0D711B7DC.title: "ME样板供应器&7[ME Pattern Provider]&f"
	task.38E290AC5E011888.title: "ME致密智能线缆&7[ME Dense Smart Cables]&f"
	task.408C5263C4664195.title: "箱子&7[Chests]&f"
	task.40A7CC56DACC2623.title: "ME玻璃线缆&7[ME Glass Cables]&f"
	task.4C5435BE5560E71B.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.61D93B13D496547D.title: "流体存储&7[Fluid Storage]&f"
	task.64EAD3DE84E94F02.title: "ME包覆线缆&7[ME Covered Cables]&f"
	task.65C439FD14C5EEB9.title: "&a便携存储&f&7[Portable Storage]&f"
	task.7241918F270CA402.title: "&aME接口&f&7[ME Interface]&f"
	task.729773FF26CBB542.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.75924053D6F5B242.title: "空间&a存储单元&f&7[Spatial Storage Cells]&f"
	task.7E0D9E6342295AB0.title: "关于频道的前言&7[Foreword on Channels]&f"
	task.7FC3DAA1BD5016A0.title: "ME智能线缆&7[ME Smart Cables]&f"
	quest.0043ED1E4EF2D4A1.quest_desc: ["这些对于提升你的能力很有用.\\n&7[These are useful for boosting your abilities.]&f"]
	quest.0043ED1E4EF2D4A1.quest_subtitle: "辅助角色&7[The support characters]&f"
	quest.0043ED1E4EF2D4A1.title: "&5其他法杖核心&7[Other Foci]&f"
	quest.04987E54ADC2C057.title: "&6德莱米护符&7[Drygmy Charm]&f"
	quest.04D9F6587EF8D9B7.quest_desc: ["&9&a药水罐&f&r最多可存储100瓶药水.你可以通过使用空瓶或药水烧瓶右键点击罐子来取出药水.\\n\\n威克西会在自动药水合成时使用这些罐子.\\n&7[The Potion Jar stores up to 100 potions. You can remove them by using an empty bottle or a potion flask on the jar. \\n\\nWixies will use these jars during Potion Autocrafting.]&f"]
	quest.04D9F6587EF8D9B7.quest_subtitle: "存储药水&7[Storing Potions]&f"
	quest.088FCB5267CB7A89.quest_desc: ["这条腰带会在短时间内给予随机的正面药水效果.这些效果的强度会有所不同.\\n&7[This belt will give random positive potion effects for a short duration. These will vary in strength.]&f"]
	quest.088FCB5267CB7A89.title: "&c不稳定馈赠腰带&7[Belt of Unstable Gifts]&f"
	quest.0A1ABE9CF7740AAA.quest_desc: ["折扣戒指提供少量最大魔力和魔力回复加成.它还能降低施放法术的总消耗.\\n&7[The Rings of Discount provides a small bonus to max mana and mana regen. It also reduces the total cost to cast a spell.]&f"]
	quest.0A1ABE9CF7740AAA.title: "&3折扣戒指&7[Rings of Discount]&f"
	quest.0D330FAD6C993DBC.quest_desc: ["这是你的法术书的下一级升级!\\n\\n这将增加你的总体魔力和魔力回复,并允许你创建和使用2级符文.\\n&7[This is the next upgrade to your Spellbook! \\n\\nThis will increase your overall mana and mana regen, as well as allowing you to create and use Tier 2 Glyphs.]&f"]
	quest.0D330FAD6C993DBC.quest_subtitle: "版本2&7[V2]&f"
	quest.0D330FAD6C993DBC.title: "&5法师的&a法术书&f&7[Mage's Spell Book]&f"
	quest.0DA31E972F2DE8AB.quest_desc: ["法杖核心以多种不同方式增强特定类型的魔法.你可以通过将鼠标悬停在符文上并查看右上角来查看法术的类型.\\n&7[Foci boost magic of a particular type in many different ways. You can see which type a spell is by hovering over the glyph and looking at the top right.]&f"]
	quest.0DA31E972F2DE8AB.quest_subtitle: "”次级偏向”&7[\"Lesser bias\"]&f"
	quest.0DA31E972F2DE8AB.title: "&9次级&a元素核心&f&7[Lesser Elemental Foci]&f"
	quest.0E2AD156E5EF263A.quest_desc: ["用于在抄写台上铭刻法术.\\n&7[Used to inscribe spells on with the Scribe's Table.]&f"]
	quest.0E2AD156E5EF263A.quest_subtitle: "花式纸张&7[Fancy Paper]&f"
	quest.0E2AD156E5EF263A.title: "&d&a法术羊皮纸&f&7[Spell Parchment]&f"
	quest.111649D7E16D869F.quest_desc: ["&9施法者魔杖&r只接受一个法术,并使用抄写台进行铭刻.\\n\\n魔杖法术总是以抛射物 > 加速开始,并且必须铭刻一个没有其他施法方式(如接触、自身等)的法术.\\n\\n这允许你施放超出10个法术上限的法术.如果你想使用破坏法术,只需将魔杖单独铭刻上破坏法术.\\n&7[The Caster's Wand only accepts a single spell, and is inscribed using the Scribe's Table. \\n\\nWand spells always start with Projectile > Accelerate, and MUST be inscribed with a spell that does not have another method (like touch, self, etc). \\n\\nThis allows you to cast spells beyond the 10 spell cap. If you want to use Break, just inscribe the wand with Break by itself.]&f"]
	quest.111649D7E16D869F.title: "&d附魔师魔杖&7[Enchanter's Wand]&f"
	quest.1322CDAC5D3007BA.quest_desc: ["现在这个比较复杂.首先,通过与一个4级&5可疑巫师&r交易并从代币制作,获得一个德莱米护符.你可以用它右键点击&2&a苔石&f&r来创建一个&2德莱米石阵&r,这会生成一个德莱米.\\n\\n这就是你的禁锢罐发挥作用的地方.启动禁锢仪式,放置禁锢罐和任何你想要获取战利品的生物.你还需要一些&d魔源&r.这应该会把生物放入罐中.\\n\\n最后,将罐子放在德莱米10格范围内,并在&2石阵&r旁边放一个满的&d魔源罐&r和一个箱子.你应该会看到罐子冒出绿色粒子,最终生物掉落物会出现在箱子里.\\n\\n关于具体速率如何计算,请阅读维基.\\n&7[Now this ones complicated. First, obtain a drygmy charm by trading with a Lv4 Shady Wizard and crafting it from the token. You can right-click Mossy Cobblestone with it to create a Drygmy Henge, which spawns a Drygmy.\\n\\nHere's where your containment jar comes in. Start the containment ritual, and place the containment jar and any mob whose loot you want to farm. You'll need some Source as well. This should put the mob in the jar.\\n\\nFinally, place the jar within 10 blocks of the drygmy, and put a full source jar and a chest next to the Henge. You should see green particles coming from the jar, and eventually the mob drops should appear in the chest.\\n\\nFor specifics on how the rates are calculated, read the wiki.]&f"]
	quest.1322CDAC5D3007BA.quest_subtitle: "甚至对Boss也有效&7[Even works for bosses]&f"
	quest.1322CDAC5D3007BA.title: "&6德莱米养殖&7[Drygmy Farming]&f"
	quest.14DB8A515CA50932.quest_desc: ["&9附魔师之剑&r允许你将一个接触法术附加到剑上.\\n\\n剑上的所有法术都会对法术的最后一个效果获得1个额外的增幅增强.\\n\\n要将法术应用到剑上,请使用抄写台.创建一个不使用施法形式的法术.\\n&7[The Enchanter's Sword allows you to attach a Touch Spell to the sword. \\n\\nAll spells on the Sword gain 1 additional Amplify augment to the last effect on the spell. \\n\\nTo apply a spell to the sword, use a Scribe's Table. Create the spell without using a form.]&f"]
	quest.14DB8A515CA50932.title: "&9附魔师之剑&7[Enchanter's Sword]&f"
	quest.151648179684B088.quest_desc: ["&a符文粉笔&f用于在地面上绘制永久性的符文.这些符文会对走过其上的实体施放法术.\\n\\n要将法术附加到符文上,请使用抄写台铭刻一张&e&a法术羊皮纸&f&r.\\n\\n注意:符文需要魔源才能运作.\\n&7[Runic Chalk is used to draw permanent Runes on that ground. These runes will cast spells on entities that walk over them. \\n\\nTo attach a spell to a rune, inscribe a Spell Parchment using a Scribe's Table.\\n\\nNote: The Rune will need Source to operate.]&f"]
	quest.151648179684B088.quest_subtitle: "可放置的法术&7[Placeable Spells]&f"
	quest.151648179684B088.title: "&6&a符文粉笔&f&7[Runic Chalk]&f"
	quest.1631AD6036F80333.quest_desc: ["你可以使用&6&d资源蜜蜂&f&r来节省宝贵的时间和空间!尽快获得它.\\n&7[You can use Productive Bees to save precious time and space! Get it as soon as possible.]&f"]
	quest.1631AD6036F80333.quest_subtitle: "比灌注室更好&7[Better than imbuement chambers]&f"
	quest.1631AD6036F80333.title: "&5自动化&a魔源水晶&f&7[Automating Source Gems]&f"
	quest.17D7D34F519F7E5F.quest_desc: ["要创建你法术书的最终等级,你需要杀死&6&a荒野奇美拉&f&r.\\n\\n这是一个&a魔法仪式&f,你需要使用&9&a仪式火盆&f&r来完成.\\n&7[To create the final tier of your Spellbook, you'll need to have killed the Wilden Chimera. \\n\\nThis is a Ritual that you'll need to complete using a Ritual Brazier.]&f"]
	quest.17D7D34F519F7E5F.quest_subtitle: "不适合胆小的人&7[Not for the faint of heart]&f"
	quest.17D7D34F519F7E5F.title: "&6&a大法师法术书&f&7[Archmage Spell Book]&f"
	quest.18A2FBE2D4133FA2.quest_desc: ["&a奥术基座&f是&a仪式火盆&f和使用&a附魔装置&f合成物品所必需的.\\n\\n去给自己做8个吧!\\n&7[Arcane Pedestals are needed for the Ritual Brazier and crafting items with an Enchanting Apparatus. \\n\\nGo ahead and make yourself 8 of them!]&f"]
	quest.18A2FBE2D4133FA2.quest_subtitle: "花式桌子&7[Fancy Tables]&f"
	quest.18A2FBE2D4133FA2.title: "&a奥术基座&f&7[Arcane Pedestals]&f"
	quest.19D02325579F2AA8.quest_desc: ["&a火山魔源通道&f通过消耗可燃物品来生成魔源.使用&a原木&f会生成额外的魔源.\\n\\n当它燃烧物品时,会将附近的石头转化为熔岩.\\n\\n这也会生成&a熔岩睡莲&f.\\n&7[The Volcanic Sourcelink generates Source by consuming burnable items. Archwood logs will generate bonus Source. \\n\\nAs it burns items, it will convert nearby stone into lava. \\n\\nThis also generates Lava Lilys.]&f"]
	quest.19D02325579F2AA8.quest_subtitle: "附带损害&7[Collateral damage]&f"
	quest.1A26E6650D007262.quest_desc: ["来源:显然是JEI.(是的,我刚才是在讽刺,你除了煤之外用这个根本得不到任何地质矿石转换,JEI刚才只是在误导你们.这个有不同路径.)\\n&7[Source: JEI, apparently. (and yes, I was being sarcastic there, you are NOT getting any GeOre conversions other than coal with this one, JEI was just gaslighting you all there. There are different paths for this.)]&f"]
	quest.1A26E6650D007262.quest_subtitle: "绝对、肯定、100%会将你的&a叵得块&f转换为萌芽地质矿石&7[Will totally, absolutely, 100% convert your 难得素 Blocks into Budding GeOre]&f"
	quest.1D86B2E553503E53.quest_desc: ["&6&a支配之杖&f&r用于控制你在世界中可能遇到的生物!每个生物对魔杖的反应都不同,所以一定要在《磨损的笔记》中查阅!\\n&7[The Dominion Wand is used for controlling the creatures you might encounter in the world! Each being responds differently to the wand, so make sure to read up in the Worn Notebook!]&f"]
	quest.1D86B2E553503E53.quest_subtitle: "友好的帮手&7[Friendly helpers]&f"
	quest.1D86B2E553503E53.title: "&6召唤帮手!&7[Summoning Help!]&f"
	quest.21B43DA96BAD42A6.quest_desc: ["&5难得素&a魔源罐&f&r可以容纳100,000魔源,而不是普通魔源罐可怜的10,000.它也是&d&a创造魔源罐&f的合成材料.\\n&7[Unobtainum Source Jar can hold 100,000 source, rather than the measly 10,000 provided by a normal one. It is also an ingredient in the Creative Source Jar.]&f"]
	quest.21B43DA96BAD42A6.quest_subtitle: "稀土金属是……有魔力的&7[Rare earth metals are...magical]&f"
	quest.21B43DA96BAD42A6.title: "&5难得素&a魔源罐&f&7[Unobtainum Source Jar]&f"
	quest.227DBA8836021B0B.quest_desc: ["在&d新生魔艺&f中,机器的能量系统被称为&9魔源&r.\\n\\n要开始收集一些魔源,我们需要一个&a魔源罐&f.\\n\\n魔源也可以用桶移动,或者通过破坏并拾取&a魔源罐&f来移动.\\n&7[In Ars Nouveau, the power system for machines is called Source. \\n\\nTo start collecting some Source, we'll need a Source Jar. \\n\\nSource can also be moved with buckets, or by breaking and picking up Source Jars.]&f"]
	quest.227DBA8836021B0B.quest_subtitle: "存储魔源&7[Storing Source]&f"
	quest.252F320615FA2839.quest_desc: ["有想要持续击中一个地方的法术吗？把它指向你想去的任何地方,抛射物就会&a反弹&r到那里.\\n&7[Have spells you want to hit at one place consistently? Point this wherever you want and projectiles will bounce straight there.]&f"]
	quest.252F320615FA2839.quest_subtitle: "反转卡牌&7[Uno reverse card]&f"
	quest.25B98F334ECF79BD.quest_desc: ["一个依靠内部时钟而非红石运行的炮塔.\\n&7[A turret that runs on an internal clock rather than redstone.]&f"]
	quest.25B98F334ECF79BD.quest_subtitle: "自动法术&7[Automatic spells]&f"
	quest.25B98F334ECF79BD.title: "&e定时法术炮塔&7[Timer Spell Turret]&f"
	quest.292A382E323B8A39.quest_desc: ["来自&d&lArs Additions&r的&6护符&r是提供各种保护和实用效果的魔法饰品.它们可以用&d魔源&r充能,并提供广泛的好处,例如消除火焰伤害、防止死亡或允许你在水下呼吸.\\n&7[Charms from the lArs Additions are magical trinkets that provide various protective and utility effects. They can be recharged with Source and offer a wide range of benefits, such as nullifying fire damage, preventing death, or allowing you to breathe underwater.]&f"]
	quest.292A382E323B8A39.title: "&6功能护符&7[Functional Charms]&f"
	quest.295C77EEC89000FC.quest_subtitle: "从生物死亡和动物繁殖中生成魔源&7[Generates Source from Mob Deaths and Animal Breeding]&f"
	quest.2C47C9B566A63135.title: "&a旋叶灵护符&7[Whirlsprig Charm]&f"
	quest.2D0CF18C8B2ABB7D.quest_desc: ["将其放置在生长的植物或树苗附近会提供魔源.奥术木树提供更多魔源!\\n\\n注意:使用骨粉不会产生魔源.\\n&7[Placing this near growing plants or saplings will provide Source. Archwood trees provide more Source! \\n\\nNote: Bonemealing does not produce Source.]&f"]
	quest.2D0CF18C8B2ABB7D.quest_subtitle: "利用植物生长创造魔源&7[Creates Source using the growth of Plants]&f"
	quest.3142A40E1EAEBAA3.quest_desc: ["&6&a探矿杆&f&r在使用时给予你魔法幸运和探知效果.\\n\\n这让你能够看到附近的魔法生物,并帮助你找到紫水晶!\\n&7[The Dowsing Rod gives you Magic Find and Scrying when used. \\n\\nThis allows you to see nearby magic creatures as well as helping you find amethyst!]&f"]
	quest.3142A40E1EAEBAA3.quest_subtitle: "魔法探测器&7[Magic Finder]&f"
	quest.3182E8AF755104E4.quest_desc: ["当格挡伤害时,&9附魔师盾牌&r会在短时间内给予使用者&a魔力再生&f和&a法术伤害提升&f效果.\\n\\n此外,盾牌会随着时间的推移,使用佩戴者的魔力进行自我修复.\\n&7[When blocking damage, the Enchanter's Shield will give the user Mana Regen and Spell Damage for a short amount of time. \\n\\nAdditionally, the shield will repair itself over time using the wearer's mana.]&f"]
	quest.3182E8AF755104E4.title: "&5附魔师盾牌&7[Enchanter's Shield]&f"
	quest.33682F4B44950123.quest_desc: ["为了获得更多的法术知识,我们需要一种特定类型的魔法木材!\\n&7[To gain further knowledge of spells, we'll need a specific type of magical wood!]&f"]
	quest.33682F4B44950123.quest_subtitle: "花式木材&7[Fancy Wood]&f"
	quest.33682F4B44950123.title: "&9奥术木&7[Archwood]&f"
	quest.34A173721735401B.title: "&d&a薇克精护符&f&7[Wixie Charm]&f"
	quest.36CDA39C23D3AA2B.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r创作,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均采用&e保留所有权利&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非该团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到此信息,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.3AE659C0C3850002.quest_desc: ["干灵侏儒以&a经验宝石&r的形式收集经验!它们用处不大,所以请随意使用!\\n&7[Drygmies farm xp in the form of experience gems! They don't have much use, so feel free to use em!]&f"]
	quest.3AE659C0C3850002.quest_subtitle: "固化经验&7[Solidified XP]&f"
	quest.3AE659C0C3850002.title: "&a经验&7[Experience]&f"
	quest.3CAB80B2BB5C2C37.quest_desc: ["过滤符文允许你将法术设置为针对特定类型的目标.\\n&7[Filter Glyphs allow you to set your spells to specific types of targets.]&f"]
	quest.3CAB80B2BB5C2C37.title: "&6过滤符文&7[Filter Glyphs]&f"
	quest.3D4D88B8BE881351.quest_desc: ["如果你想施放更好的法术,你需要一个&6抄写台&r来为你的法术书&a解锁&f新符文.\\n\\n符文有3个等级可&a解锁&f,每个等级都需要一些经验和物品.\\n\\n抄写台也用于将法术附着到&a法术羊皮纸&f上.为此,将一张&a法术羊皮纸&f放在台上,在你的法术书中选择法术,然后潜行右键点击台上的书.\\n\\n要创建一个符文,用你的法术书右键点击抄写台.搜索你想要制作的符文,然后点击底部的”选择”.用所需的物品右键点击台子,符文就会被创建.使用符文来学习它.\\n\\n注意:台子可以从附近的容器中提取物品.\\n&7[If you want to cast better spells, you'll need a Scribe's Table to unlock new glyphs for your spellbook. \\n\\nThere are 3 tiers of glyphs to unlock, and each one requires some experience and items. \\n\\nThe Scribe's Table is also used to attach spells to Spell Parchments. To do this, place a Spell Parchment on the table, select the spell in your Spellbook, then sneak right-click the book on the table. \\n\\nTo create a Glyph, right-click on the Scribe's Table with your spellbook. Search for the glyph you want to make, then click Select at the bottom. Right-click the table with the items required, and the glyph will be created. Use the glyph to learn it. \\n\\nNote: The table can pull items from nearby inventories.]&f"]
	quest.3D4D88B8BE881351.quest_subtitle: "升级法术&7[Upgrading Spells]&f"
	quest.3D4D88B8BE881351.title: "&6抄写台&7[Scribe's Table]&f"
	quest.3D862A3D3F83CA26.quest_desc: [
		"&9&a附魔装置&f&r用于制作模组内的各种物品.它需要魔源才能工作.\\n\\n它也是一个多方块结构,利用&a奥术基座&f进行合成.\\n\\n首先在地上放置一个&a奥术核心&f,然后将&a附魔装置&f放在它上面.用&a奥术基座&f围绕附魔装置.\\n\\n&7[The Enchanting Apparatus is used to craft various items within the mod. It requires Source to work.\\n\\nIt is also a multiblock structure that utilizes Arcane Pedestals to craft.\\n\\nStart by placing an Arcane Core in the ground, then place the Enchanting Apparatus on top of it. Surround the Apparatus with Arcane Pedestals.\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/ars/enchanting_app.png width:200 height:175 align:1}"
	]
	quest.3D862A3D3F83CA26.quest_subtitle: "花式合成&7[Fancy Crafting]&f"
	quest.3D862A3D3F83CA26.title: "&9&a附魔装置&f&7[Enchanting Apparatus]&f"
	quest.3DEF6BC2C123E676.quest_desc: ["一个可调节的版本,使用&6&a支配之杖&f&r,一如既往.也接受所有即将出现的那些酷炫透镜.\\n&7[An adjustable version, with the Dominion Wand, as always. Also accepts all of those cool lenses that are coming up.]&f"]
	quest.3DEF6BC2C123E676.quest_subtitle: "那是针对性的&7[That was targeted]&f"
	quest.3FD702B5AB006402.quest_desc: ["你是否曾想过无论走到哪里都能悬浮？\\n\\n这个腰带允许你漂浮.要激活,只需在空中潜行,无论是下落时还是跳跃后.\\n&7[Have you ever wanted to just hover everywhere you go? \\n\\nThis belt allows you to levitate. To activate, just sneak while in the air, either while falling or from jumping.]&f"]
	quest.3FD702B5AB006402.title: "&9&a浮空腰带&f&7[Belt of Levitation]&f"
	quest.40321FBF721ACF46.quest_desc: ["不言自明的升级,它们...&4相当破坏平衡&r.自己看看吧...\\n&7[Self-explanatory upgrades that are...pretty broken. See for yourself...]&f"]
	quest.40321FBF721ACF46.quest_subtitle: "提升你的偏转能力&7[Boosting your deflections]&f"
	quest.40BC67BDEE15D1DE.quest_desc: ["要制作&a魔源水晶&f,我们需要将青金石或&a紫水晶碎片&f放入&a灌注室&f.随着时间的推移,这些会转化为&a魔源水晶&f!\\n&7[To create Source Gems, we'll need to put either Lapis or Amethyst Shards into the Imbuement Chamber. Over time, these will convert to Source Gems!]&f"]
	quest.40BC67BDEE15D1DE.quest_subtitle: "Ars的铁&7[The iron of Ars]&f"
	quest.40BC67BDEE15D1DE.title: "&d&a魔源水晶&f&7[Source Gems]&f"
	quest.41A0BE357C8A74E1.quest_desc: ["&9&a炼金魔源通道&f&r从相邻的药水瓶中产生魔源.\\n\\n魔源量因药水和复杂度而异.\\n&7[The Alchemical Sourcelink produces Source from adjacent potion jars. \\n\\nThe amount of source varies per potion and complexity.]&f"]
	quest.41A0BE357C8A74E1.quest_subtitle: "通过药水供能&7[Power through Potions]&f"
	quest.441C0659ED28D935.quest_desc: ["一级符文需要3级经验来制作.\\n&7[Tier 1 Glyphs require 3 levels of experience to be made.]&f"]
	quest.441C0659ED28D935.title: "&a一级符文&7[Tier 1 Glyphs]&f"
	quest.457DE8C154641437.quest_desc: ["&9&a仪式火盆&f&r用于举行仪式.它也可以用于装饰.如果你想点燃火盆,对它使用光亮法术.\\n\\n要举行仪式,你还需要&a奥术基座&f.由于有太多仪式可以举行,请务必使用&6磨损的笔记&r查看每一个!\\n\\n这可以通过在物品栏中有书时,按住Ctrl键点击&a仪式台&f来完成.\\n&7[The Ritual Brazier is used to cast rituals. It can also be used for decoration. If you want to light the Brazier, use a Light spell on it. \\n\\nTo perform rituals, you'll need Arcane Pedestals as well. As there are so many rituals to cast, make sure to check out each of them using the Worn Notebook! \\n\\nThis can be done by holding Ctrl on the Ritual Table while the book is in your inventory.]&f"]
	quest.457DE8C154641437.quest_subtitle: "我发誓这不是邪教...&7[It's not a cult I swear...]&f"
	quest.457DE8C154641437.title: "&9&a仪式火盆&f&7[Ritual Brazier]&f"
	quest.47DD9F268BC2254E.quest_desc: ["现在我们有了枪!来自&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r的&5基础法术炮塔&r是一个方块,当它接收到红石信号时会施放一个预先铭刻的法术.它的功能类似于发射器,但用于法术,从附近的&5&a魔源罐&f&r中汲取必要的魔源来为施法供能.\\n&7[Now we have guns! The Basic Spell Turret from lArs Nouveau is a block that casts a pre-inscribed spell when it receives a redstone signal. It functions similarly to a dispenser but for spells, drawing the necessary source from nearby Source Jars to power the cast.]&f"]
	quest.47DD9F268BC2254E.quest_subtitle: "咻咻&7[Pew pew]&f"
	quest.47DD9F268BC2254E.title: "&5基础法术炮塔&7[Basic Spell Turret]&f"
	quest.48A5B5FBAFD3AED7.quest_subtitle: "威力更大&7[Packs a greater punch]&f"
	quest.48A5B5FBAFD3AED7.title: "&a压缩经验&7[Compressed Experience]&f"
	quest.48A6087A6EAD6A85.title: "&b&a塞壬护符&f&7[Siren Charm]&f"
	quest.48D5D9D9AD98409F.title: "&6星宝石护符&7[Starbuncle Charm]&f"
	quest.48D8E1B9D76BAFC1.quest_desc: ["来自&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r模组的&6手镯&r是一种饰品,具体来说是一件魔法装备,提供特殊的被动能力,并可用于提升法术伤害.它们可以被制作并佩戴,以赋予基于元素的效果并增强你的魔法力量.\\n&7[Bangles from the lArs Nouveau mod are a type of bauble, specifically a piece of magical equipment that provides special passive abilities and can be used to boost spell damage. They can be crafted and worn to grant elemental-based effects and enhance your magical power.]&f"]
	quest.48D8E1B9D76BAFC1.title: "&6手镯&7[Bangles]&f"
	quest.4D4D383E210A4897.quest_desc: ["来自&d&lArs&r的&5精华&r是另一个极其重要的材料.你几乎每个法术和附魔装置配方都需要它.\\n&7[Essence from lArs is another extremely important material. You need it for virtually every spell and enchanting apparatus recipe.]&f"]
	quest.4D4D383E210A4897.quest_subtitle: "你会需要这些...&7[You'll need these...]&f"
	quest.4D4D383E210A4897.title: "&2Ars&r &9精&r&4华&r&6&7[Ars Essence]&f"
	quest.51162B9185A45BB1.quest_desc: ["这把弓可以使用抄写台铭刻一个法术.\\n\\n以魔力为代价,箭矢会变成&a法术箭矢&f,并对目标施加法术.\\n\\n如果你没有箭矢,会施放一个造成0点伤害的法术箭.如果魔力不足,则会发射普通箭矢.\\n\\n&9附魔弓&r也可以使用特殊的强化箭矢来增强铭刻的法术.\\n&7[This bow can be inscribed with a spell using a Scribe's Table. \\n\\nAt the cost of mana, arrows will become Spell Arrows and will apply the spell on their target. \\n\\nIf you have no arrows, a spell arrow that deals 0 damage will be cast. If there is not enough mana, regular arrows will be fired instead. \\n\\nThe Enchanter's Bow can also use special Augment Arrows that empower the inscribed spell.]&f"]
	quest.51162B9185A45BB1.title: "&5附魔弓&7[Enchanter's Bow]&f"
	quest.542C6D76B579886C.quest_desc: ["使用那些种子,我们将要制作我们的第一种纤维,&5&a法师之花纤维&f&r.\\n\\n这将用于为我们制作一些魔法饰品!\\n&7[Using those seeds, we'll want to craft our first fiber, the Magebloom Fiber. \\n\\nThis will be used to create us some magical accessories!]&f"]
	quest.542C6D76B579886C.quest_subtitle: "花式线&7[Fancy String]&f"
	quest.542C6D76B579886C.title: "&d&a法师之花纤维&f&7[Magebloom Fiber]&f"
	quest.54954F1FF453CAA2.quest_desc: ["These are formidable weapons to go against. They will shoot super-charged spells when the spell is aligned with its element.\\n\\nHint: works best on defense."]
	quest.54954F1FF453CAA2.quest_subtitle: "防御的王者&7[The boss of defense]&f"
	quest.54954F1FF453CAA2.title: "&6元素炮塔&7[Elemental Turrets]&f"
	quest.555B604217D266AF.quest_desc: ["曾想过移动魔源吗？你很幸运!&3&a末影魔源罐&f&r是一个纠缠的&d&a魔源罐&f&r,用&d&a支配之杖&f&r链接它们也会链接它们的魔源容量,提供即时传输.\\n&7[Ever wanted to move source around? You're in luck! The Ender Source Jar is an entangled Source Jar where linking them with a Dominion Wand will also link their source capacity, providing instant transport.]&f"]
	quest.555B604217D266AF.quest_subtitle: "自动化永无止境&7[Automation for days]&f"
	quest.555B604217D266AF.title: "&3&a末影魔源罐&f&7[Ender Source Jar]&f"
	quest.5766C8B9E850C186.quest_desc: [
		"要制作Ars中的主要合成物品之一,&9&a魔源水晶&f&r,我们需要制作一个&6&a灌注室&f&r.\\n\\n&a灌注室&f需要魔源来灌注物品.它自身会产生少量魔源,但也可以使用&a魔源罐&f作为能源.\\n\\n一些配方还需要在其周围放置&a奥术基座&f.\\n\\n&7[To create one of the main crafting items in Ars, the Source Gem, we'll need to make an Imbuement Chamber. \\n\\nThe Imbuement Chamber requires Source to imbue items. It produces a small amount of Source by itself, but can also use Source Jars as a power source. \\n\\nSeveral recipes also require Arcane Pedestals to be placed around it as well.\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/ars/imbuement.png width:200 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.5766C8B9E850C186.quest_subtitle: "制作&a魔源水晶&f&7[Creating Source Gems]&f"
	quest.5766C8B9E850C186.title: "&6&a灌注室&f&7[Imbuement Chamber]&f"
	quest.57C316D02DA833CE.quest_subtitle: "有时有帮助,有时没有&7[Sometimes helpful, sometimes not]&f"
	quest.57C316D02DA833CE.title: "&a晶矿傀儡&f&7[GeOre Golems]&f"
	quest.58EC47584C773B82.quest_desc: ["使用我们的&a附魔装置&f结构,我们将要制作我们的第一颗种子,&5&a法师之花种子&f&r.\\n\\n这将用于为我们制作一些魔法服装!\\n&7[Using our Enchanting Apparatus structure, we'll want to craft our first seed, the Magebloom Seed. \\n\\nThis will be used to create us some magical clothing!]&f"]
	quest.58EC47584C773B82.quest_subtitle: "种植魔法&7[Growing Magic]&f"
	quest.58EC47584C773B82.title: "&5&a法师之花种子&f&7[Magebloom Seed]&f"
	quest.5AEFB843AA0A575E.quest_desc: ["用于制作&d&l&a元素魔艺&f&r中的许多高级物品.\\n&7[Used to make much of the advanced items from lArs Elemental.]&f"]
	quest.5AEFB843AA0A575E.quest_subtitle: "仅限大师&7[Masters only]&f"
	quest.5AEFB843AA0A575E.title: "&5大师符石&7[Mark of Mastery]&f"
	quest.5C3FF43CF16BCF30.quest_desc: ["有了&a魔源水晶&f,你可以通过制作&5魔源石&r来开始制作各种机器.\\n&7[With Source Gems, you can get started crafting the various machines by creating Sourcestones.]&f"]
	quest.5C3FF43CF16BCF30.quest_subtitle: "以前称为”&a奥术石材&f”&7[Formerly \"Arcane Stones\"]&f"
	quest.5C3FF43CF16BCF30.title: "&5魔源石&7[Sourcestone]&f"
	quest.5CFBA24B3E0CDEDD.quest_desc: [
		"手持法术书时,你可以按C键打开法术创建页面.\\n\\n每个法术必须有一个形态.你从3个基本形态开始:投射物、自身施放和接触.\\n\\n至于效果,这决定了你施放法术时会发生什么.每个法术最多可以有9个效果.\\n\\n对于初学者,你有伤害和破坏.\\n\\n选择一个形态和一个效果,命名你的法术,然后点击创建!\\n&7[While holding your Spellbook, you can press C to open up the spell creation page. \\n\\nEach spell must have a form. You start off with 3 basic forms: Projectile, Self-cast, and Touch. \\n\\nFor the Effect, this determines what happens when you cast the spell. You can have up to 9 effects per spell. \\n\\nFor starters, you have Harm and Break. \\n\\nSelect one Form and one Effect, name your spell, and click create!]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/ars/spellbook.png width:200 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.5CFBA24B3E0CDEDD.quest_subtitle: "你是个巫师,哈利!&7[You're a wizard, Harry!]&f"
	quest.5CFBA24B3E0CDEDD.title: "&3创建你的第一个法术&7[Creating Your First Spell]&f"
	quest.6165B87E2B8D2021.quest_desc: ["这些是更强大和增强的法杖核心版本.\\n&7[These are the more enchanced and powerful versions of foci.]&f"]
	quest.6165B87E2B8D2021.quest_subtitle: "偏见的极致&7[Bias at its finest]&f"
	quest.6165B87E2B8D2021.title: "&c&a元素核心&f&7[Elemental Foci]&f"
	quest.632BC46928CC9A8C.quest_desc: ["&9附魔镜&r在使用时会施加一个自身法术.\\n\\n用这面镜子施放的法术会打折并获得额外的持续时间加成.\\n\\n要施加一个法术,使用抄写台.创建一个不使用形态的法术.\\n&7[The Enchanter's Mirror will apply a self spell when used. \\n\\nSpells cast with this mirror are discounted and gain additional bonus duration. \\n\\nTo apply a spell, use a Scribe's table. Create a spell without using a form.]&f"]
	quest.632BC46928CC9A8C.title: "&d附魔镜&7[Enchanter's Mirror]&f"
	quest.63DD7F5A4441ACE7.quest_desc: ["二级符文需要5级经验来制作.\\n\\n它们还需要一本&9法师&a法术书&f&r来创建.\\n&7[Tier 2 Glyphs require 5 levels of experience to be made. \\n\\nThey also require a Mage's Spell Book to create.]&f"]
	quest.63DD7F5A4441ACE7.title: "&e二级符文&7[Tier 2 Glyphs]&f"
	quest.644FECEAE63D9938.title: "&c火焰炮护符&7[Firecannon Charm]&f"
	quest.64D0E66CB4FBEC82.quest_desc: ["要开始,你需要为自己制作一本&6新手法术书&r!\\n\\n这是你创建和存储法术的地方.\\n\\n按&9C&r键将打开”创建法术”页面.左侧有几个标签页,但主要的3个是:法术创建、&a拾色器&f和使魔.\\n\\n这本法术书只允许你创建和使用一级符文.要创建更好的法术,你需要升级你的法术书!\\n&7[To get started, you'll need to craft yourself a Novice Spellbook! \\n\\nThis is where you create and store your spells. \\n\\nHitting the C key will open up the 'Create a Spell' page. On the left, there are several tabs, but the main 3 are: Spell Creation, Color Picker, and Familiars. \\n\\nThis spellbook will only allow you to create and use Tier 1 Glyphs. To create better spells, you'll need to upgrade your Spellbook!]&f"]
	quest.64D0E66CB4FBEC82.quest_subtitle: "我们的第一本法术书&7[Our First Spellbook]&f"
	quest.64D0E66CB4FBEC82.title: "&a法术书&f&7[Spell Books]&f"
	quest.671B67E617D56184.quest_desc: ["一个你可以随意瞄准的炮塔.\\n&7[A turret that you can aim wherever you like.]&f"]
	quest.671B67E617D56184.quest_subtitle: "瞄准&7[Aiming]&f"
	quest.671B67E617D56184.title: "&9可调节法术炮塔&7[Adjustable Spell Turret]&f"
	quest.6877742C20B7A40B.quest_desc: ["现在我们说到点子上了.不幸的是,其他四种精华还没有蜜蜂...\\n&7[Now we're talking. Unfortunately the other four essences don't have bees yet...]&f"]
	quest.6877742C20B7A40B.quest_subtitle: "一个简单的改进&7[A simple improvement]&f"
	quest.6877742C20B7A40B.title: "&2自动化&r &3精华&7[Automating Essence]&f"
	quest.6A1C0B17B22CE50F.quest_desc: ["&9&a魔力提升护身符&f&r提升最大魔力.\\n\\n&6&a魔力再生护身符&f&r提升你的魔力恢复速度.\\n&7[The Amulet of Mana Boost gives a boost to max mana. \\n\\nThe Amulet of Mana Regen gives a boost to your mana regen.]&f"]
	quest.6A1C0B17B22CE50F.title: "&c&a护符&f&7[The Amulets]&f"
	quest.6B511C8B572E8940.quest_desc: ["在屏幕的左下角,你会看到一个条.这个条就是你的魔力池!\\n\\n有几种方法可以增加你的魔力池,或者随着你在模组中的进展提高法术的效率.升级你的法术书也可以增加你的魔力!\\n&7[In the bottom left of your screen, you'll see a bar. This bar is your mana pool! \\n\\nThere are several ways to increase your mana pool, or increase the efficiency of your spells as you progress through the mod. Upgrading your spellbook can also increase your mana!]&f"]
	quest.6B511C8B572E8940.quest_subtitle: "&a魔能&f&7[Mage Power]&f"
	quest.6B511C8B572E8940.title: "&5魔力&7[Mana]&f"
	quest.6CEAA86EEAAC1203.title: "&5&a紫晶傀儡护符&f&7[Amethyst Golem Charm]&f"
	quest.6DAA82B5F94AF9F8.quest_desc: ["&9&a光之瓶&f&r召唤一个跟随你的漂浮光源.\\n\\n&6&a湮灭之瓶&f&r以魔力为代价销毁你拾取的物品.这可以过滤.\\n\\n要添加或移除被瓶子销毁的物品,用副手持有该物品使用瓶子,或者在抄写台上放置瓶子,然后用物品右键点击台子.\\n\\n瓶子必须在你的快捷栏中才能生效.\\n&7[The Jar of Light summons a floating light source that follows you. \\n\\nThe Jar of Voiding destroys items you pick up in exchange for mana. This can be filtered. \\n\\nTo add or remove an item to be destroyed by the jar, use the jar with the item in your off hand, or use an item on the Scribe's Table with the jar placed on it. \\n\\nThe jar must be on your hotbar to function.]&f"]
	quest.6DAA82B5F94AF9F8.title: "&b瓶子们&7[The Jars]&f"
	quest.6E0E13806F388D7E.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到&a&d新生魔艺&f&f!\\n\\n&d新生魔艺&f是一个魔法模组,允许你使用模组内制作的不同符文来创建自定义法术!\\n&7[Welcome to Ars Nouveau! \\n\\nArs Nouveau is a magic mod that allows you to create custom spells with the different Glyphs made within the mod!]&f"]
	quest.6E0E13806F388D7E.title: "欢迎来到&a&d新生魔艺&f&f!&7[Welcome to Ars Nouveau!]&f"
	quest.6EDA801044ED0445.quest_desc: ["这个升级后的炮塔发射更强大的法术并提升它们的威力.\\n&7[This upgraded turret shoots much more powerful spells and boosts their power.]&f"]
	quest.6EDA801044ED0445.quest_subtitle: "威力升级&7[A power upgrade]&f"
	quest.6EDA801044ED0445.title: "&d&a附魔法术炮塔&f&7[Enchanted Spell Turret]&f"
	quest.6F3602F5600A6221.quest_desc: ["三级符文需要10级经验来制作.\\n\\n它们还需要一本&6&a大法师法术书&f&r.\\n&7[Tier 3 Glyphs require 10 levels of experience to be made. \\n\\nThey also require an Archmage Spell Book.]&f"]
	quest.6F3602F5600A6221.title: "&4三级符文&7[Tier 3 Glyphs]&f"
	quest.77145113CD5B26FB.quest_desc: ["魔源浆果比其他来源产生更多的魔源.\\n\\n这也会将其周围3x3区域内的草或泥土转化为菌丝.如果空间是空的,它还会在周围生长蘑菇.\\n&7[Source Berries produce more Source than other sources. \\n\\nThis will also convert grass or dirt into Mycelium in a 3x3 area around it. It will also grow mushrooms around it if the space is empty.]&f"]
	quest.77145113CD5B26FB.quest_subtitle: "从附近食物生成魔源&7[Generates Source from Nearby Food]&f"
	task.00BEC4A28F318E6F.title: "手镯&7[Bangles]&f"
	task.01FD75641E5EA5E4.title: "魔力&7[Mana]&f"
	task.03EB390E79866058.title: "魔源石&7[Sourcestones]&f"
	task.04A97A2825505B64.title: "&a元素核心&f&7[Elemental Foci]&f"
	task.0E6876A34D1975EB.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.15C6E9C02D1FBEC0.title: "二级符文&7[Tier 2 Glyphs]&f"
	task.1B916AE67F84E6D7.title: "创建你的第一个法术&7[Creating Your First Spell]&f"
	task.1CC556A6921208B8.title: "一级符文&7[Tier 1 Glyphs]&f"
	task.2BC0F5A88E2F03C3.title: "奥术木&7[Archwood]&f"
	task.388545A0E3B4930D.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.470F4163DBE13B6B.title: "棱镜透镜&7[Prism Lenses]&f"
	task.56CA4F2E7116C934.title: "&a晶矿傀儡&f&7[GeOre Golems]&f"
	task.5B96C6088CE5EC1E.title: "功能性护符&7[Functional Charms]&f"
	task.65D68BEEB36FC805.title: "第 3 阶雕符&7[Tier 3 Glyphs]&f"
	task.6821298BA1E6D9C4.title: "过滤雕符&7[Filter Glyphs]&f"
	task.700585855857088E.title: "其他法杖核心&7[Other Foci]&f"
	task.736B8E029232D795.title: "新生魔艺精华&7[Ars Essences]&f"
	task.755006DBA2D7D500.title: "次级 &a元素核心&f&7[Lesser Elemental Foci]&f"
	task.798D6FBE32F46484.title: "元素炮塔&7[Elemental Turrets]&f"
	quest.001B195541AE0FA1.quest_desc: ["这是一套有趣的盔甲,我经常穿着它到处 &a弹跳&r 和 &a攀爬&r.\\n&7[It's a fun armor that I use for bouncing and climbing everywhere all the time.]&f"]
	quest.001B195541AE0FA1.quest_subtitle: "12&7[12]&f"
	quest.001B195541AE0FA1.title: "&a黏液盔甲&7[Slime Armor]&f"
	quest.004D61425172324F.quest_desc: ["&8&a锁链胸甲&f&r 比铁甲稍差一些.它在 &l&2Minecraft&r 中的主要用途源于其难以获取的特性,只能通过交易和 &a生物掉落&f 获得.\\n\\n当然,这是加了模组的版本,所以我们现在可以合成它了!这反而让它失去了原本的意义……\\n&7[Chainmail Armor is a little worse than Iron. Its main use in lMinecraft was its elusive nature, only being obtained through Trades and Mob Drops. \\n\\nOf course this is modded though, so we can craft it now! Which takes away its purpose...]&f"]
	quest.004D61425172324F.quest_subtitle: "12&7[12]&f"
	quest.004D61425172324F.title: "&8&a链甲胸甲&f&7[Chainmail Armor]&f"
	quest.03C059DFF8F1BF41.quest_desc: ["由 &2&lPickle Tweaks&r 模组添加的 &a绿宝石&r 盔甲提供了一套属性与钻石盔甲相似的盔甲,但基本上是免费的,因为 &a绿宝石&r 很容易获得.\\n&7[The Emerald armor added by the lPickle Tweaks mod provides an armor set with similar stats to diamond armor but basically for free, as emeralds are easy to get.]&f"]
	quest.03C059DFF8F1BF41.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.03C059DFF8F1BF41.title: "&a绿宝石盔甲&7[Emerald Armor]&f"
	quest.04B31A600004F7CB.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 编写,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 AllTheMods 团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你能看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.06B8539B731FE4BA.quest_desc: ["来自 &b&l&d戴尔设备&f&r 模组的 &4蚀空合金&r 盔甲是 &b&lJDT&r 盔甲中最终且最强大的等级.虽然它提供与钻石盔甲同等的防护,但其真正功能来自于其能量容量以及可以应用于其上的许许多多升级.\\n&7[The Eclipse Alloy armor from the lJust Dire Things mod is the final and most powerful tier of lJDT's armor. While it provides the protection of diamond armor, its real functions come from its energy capacity and many many many upgrades that can be applied to it. ]&f"]
	quest.06B8539B731FE4BA.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.06B8539B731FE4BA.title: "&4蚀空合金盔甲&7[Eclipse Alloy Armor]&f"
	quest.074EC1E636CD6605.quest_desc: ["&c下界合金盔甲&r 是 &l&2原版&r 中最好的盔甲.它拥有与 &b钻石&r 相同的 &a护甲值&f,但拥有更高的 &a盔甲韧性&f.\\n\\n大概是因为你需要 &b钻石&r 来制作它!\\n&7[Netherite Armor is the best lVanilla can get. It has same Armor Points as Diamond but more Armor Toughness. \\n\\nProbably because you need Diamond to make it!]&f"]
	quest.074EC1E636CD6605.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.074EC1E636CD6605.title: "&c下界合金盔甲&7[Netherite Armor]&f"
	quest.0ABB2264CBB82470.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l新生魔艺&r 盔甲中的 &a铁甲&f.\\n\\n&7[Iron Armor of lArs Armor.\\n]&f"
		"&5奥术师&r 套装是基础 &5&d新生魔艺&f&r 模组中三种主要魔法盔甲类型之一,另外两种是 &5巫师&r 和 &c战斗法师&r 套装.\\n\\n它提供中等数量的魔法线槽位,这些线槽能赋予特殊增益和能力.它比 &c战斗法师&r 盔甲更通用,但比 &5巫师&r 盔甲的线槽更少、威力更弱.\\n&7[The Arcanist set is one of three primary magical armor types in the base Ars Nouveau mod, alongside the Sorcerer and Battlemage sets.\\n\\nIt provides a moderate number of slots for magical threads, which grant special perks and abilities. It is more versatile than the Battlemage armor but has fewer, less powerful slots than the Sorcerer's armor. ]&f"
	]
	quest.0ABB2264CBB82470.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.0ABB2264CBB82470.title: "&5奥术师套装&7[Arcanist Outfit]&f"
	quest.0CE23DBBBFBCC372.quest_desc: ["来自 &6禁忌与奥秘&r 模组的 &6莫腾盔甲&r 是一套基础的前期盔甲,提供比皮革盔甲稍好的防护.它以其低廉的资源成本和酷炫的外观而著称,但只是一套临时使用的装备.\\n\\n&4致编辑模式用户:此任务被暂时隐藏,因为在撰写本文时莫腾盔甲缺少合成配方.当莫腾盔甲可以通过禁忌与奥秘或KubeJS合成时,请移除此注释并取消隐藏此任务.\\n&7[The Mortem Armor from the Forbidden Arcanus mod is a basic, early-game armor set that offers slightly better protection than leather armor. It is notable for its low resource cost and cool look but is only a temporary set of gear to use.\\n\\nNote to those in Editing Mode: This quest was temporarily hidden as Mortem Armor lacks a recipe at the time of writing. When Mortem Armor becomes craftable, be it via Forbidden Arcanus or KubeJS, remove this note and unhide the quest.]&f"]
	quest.0CE23DBBBFBCC372.quest_subtitle: "11&7[11]&f"
	quest.0CE23DBBBFBCC372.title: "&6莫腾盔甲&7[Mortem Armor]&f"
	quest.0E2515424291BB59.quest_desc: ["&d&l新生魔艺&r 盔甲的 &b钻石&r 版本!\\n&7[Diamond version of lArs Armors!]&f"]
	quest.0E2515424291BB59.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.0E2515424291BB59.title: "&5战斗法师套装&7[Battlemages Outfit]&f"
	quest.0F1D6F4729CC38F3.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从 &a狂猎凋灵骷髅&f 处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Hunt Wither Skeletons]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_rib.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0F1D6F4729CC38F3.quest_subtitle: "下界要塞&7[Nether Fortress]&f"
	quest.0F1D6F4729CC38F3.title: "Rib &a护甲夹板&f&7[Rib Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.10AA2B20D86747F7.quest_desc: ["&b核源铁锭&r 拥有与铁甲相同的属性,但拥有铁甲梦寐以求的其他能力!\\n\\n查看物品描述以了解更多它们能做什么!\\n&7[Ferricore has same stats as Iron but has other abilities Iron wishes it had! \\n\\nCheck out the Item descriptions to learn more of what they can do!]&f"]
	quest.10AA2B20D86747F7.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.10AA2B20D86747F7.title: "&b核源铁锭盔甲&7[Ferricore Amor]&f"
	quest.1245126B4338C019.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从野生唤魔者处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Evokers]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_vex.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1245126B4338C019.quest_subtitle: "&a林地大厦&f&7[Woodland Mansion]&f"
	quest.1245126B4338C019.title: "Vex &a护甲夹板&f&7[Vex Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.13517D17E6BF015F.quest_desc: ["用 &b钻石盔甲&r 和一些 &a下级精华物品&r,我们可以合成 &a下级精华盔甲&r!\\n\\n它们还可以通过匠魂进行升级!\\n&7[With Diamond Armor and a few Inferium Items we can craft Inferium Armor! \\n\\nThey can also be upgraded with Tinkering!]&f"]
	quest.13517D17E6BF015F.quest_subtitle: "21&7[21]&f"
	quest.13517D17E6BF015F.title: "&a下级精华盔甲&7[Inferium Armor]&f"
	quest.17A68C4E9E9EA2B7.quest_desc: ["&e金盔甲&r 正好介于铁甲和 &7皮革&r 之间.但其耐久度更接近 &7皮革&r.\\n\\n除了穿着一些 &e金盔甲&r 能让猪灵对你保持中立外,它没有太多用处.\\n&7[Golden Armor is right between Iron and Leather. But its Durability is much closer to Leather. \\n\\nThere is not much use for it besides having Piglins Neutral towards you when wearing some Gold Armor.]&f"]
	quest.17A68C4E9E9EA2B7.quest_subtitle: "11&7[11]&f"
	quest.17A68C4E9E9EA2B7.title: "&e金盔甲&7[Golden Armor]&f"
	quest.19F58E291A543228.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l新生魔艺&r 盔甲的 &e金&r 版本!\\n&7[Gold version of lArs Armors!]&f"
		""
		"这是一套 &5魔法&r 盔甲,基础防御力很低,但拥有最大的 &5魔法&r 升级潜力.与其他盔甲套装不同,它无法承受太多伤害,但能大幅提升你的法术威力.\\n\\n也许你甚至不需要给它附上经验修补……\\n&7[It is a magic armor set with very low base defense but the greatest potential for magical upgrades. Unlike the other armor sets, it cannot resist much damage but in drastically increases your spell power.\\n\\nMaybe you don't even need mending for this one...]&f"
	]
	quest.19F58E291A543228.quest_subtitle: "11&7[11]&f"
	quest.19F58E291A543228.title: "&5巫师套装&7[Sorcerer's Outfit]&f"
	quest.1A8440C0048EEB02.quest_desc: ["&c烈焰金&r 拥有与铁甲相同的属性,但拥有铁甲梦寐以求的其他能力!\\n\\n查看物品描述以了解更多它们能做什么!\\n&7[Blazegold has same stats as Iron but has other abilities Iron wishes it had! \\n\\nCheck out the Item descriptions to learn more of what they can do!]&f"]
	quest.1A8440C0048EEB02.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.1A8440C0048EEB02.title: "&c烈焰金盔甲&7[Blazegold Armor]&f"
	quest.1C27C74722A19FC1.quest_desc: ["用一大堆超级昂贵的 &l&5&d通用机械&f&r 物品,你可以将 &5难以获取盔甲&r 升级为 &aMekaSuit&r!\\n\\n现在它可以储存能量,并且受到伤害时不会损失生命值,而是消耗能量.\\n\\n你可以使用升级单元让它变得更强大!\\n&7[With a ton of super expensive lMekanism Items you can upgrade 难得素 Armor to the MekaSuit! \\n\\nNow it can hold Energy and instead of taking hearts from damage, it will take Energy. \\n\\nYou can use Upgrade Units to make it even better!]&f"]
	quest.1C27C74722A19FC1.quest_subtitle: "你能提供的最大能量&7[As much Energy you can supply]&f"
	quest.1C27C74722A19FC1.title: "&aMekaSuit 护甲&7[MekaSuit]&f"
	quest.1CC627D3FB348C89.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从野生虫群蠹虫处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Horde Silverfish]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_shaper.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1CC627D3FB348C89.quest_subtitle: "古迹废墟&7[Trail Ruins]&f"
	quest.1CC627D3FB348C89.title: "塑形 &a护甲夹板&f&7[Shaper Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.1D27EE427ECFD6CE.quest_desc: ["&c三级精华&r 的 &a增强&f 版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of Tertium.]&f"]
	quest.1D27EE427ECFD6CE.quest_subtitle: "27&7[27]&f"
	quest.1D27EE427ECFD6CE.title: "&9二级精华盔甲&7[Imperium Armor]&f"
	quest.1D91E37BFD8CC911.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_emerald.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.1D91E37BFD8CC911.title: "&2绿宝石&r&7[Emerald]&f"
	quest.1E3E688B3B52C4D2.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从野生虫群蠹虫处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Horde Silverfish]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_raiser.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1E3E688B3B52C4D2.quest_subtitle: "古迹废墟&7[Trail Ruins]&f"
	quest.1E3E688B3B52C4D2.title: "提升 &a护甲夹板&f&7[Raiser Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.1EABF2E7AE7B8F22.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_netherite.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.1EABF2E7AE7B8F22.title: "&8下界合金&r&7[Netherite]&f"
	quest.1FAE4A884E083283.quest_desc: ["来自 &d&l&d禁忌与奥秘&f&r 模组的 &6提尔盔甲&r 是该模组中最好的 &a防御&f 装备,提供强大的防护和耐久度.它是 &5龙之奥秘&r 盔甲的升级版,需要模组后期的 &6&a赫菲斯托斯锻炉&f&r.\\n&7[The Tyr armor from the lForbidden and Arcanus mod is the best defensive gear from the mod, offering strong protection and durability. It is an upgrade to the Draco Arcanus armor and requires mod's late-game Forge.]&f"]
	quest.1FAE4A884E083283.quest_subtitle: "37&7[37]&f"
	quest.1FAE4A884E083283.title: "&6提尔盔甲&7[Tyr Armor]&f"
	quest.1FC7ABEAB5018E79.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_redstone.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.1FC7ABEAB5018E79.title: "&4红石&r&7[Redstone]&f"
	quest.211FD55DEB635A98.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_copper.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.211FD55DEB635A98.title: "&6铜&r&7[Copper]&f"
	quest.2296CE4418AE62D4.quest_desc: ["&6ATM盔甲&r,但增强了 &d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r 法术!\\n&7[ATM Armor but with buffs to lArs Nouveau Spells!]&f"]
	quest.2296CE4418AE62D4.quest_subtitle: "24&7[24]&f"
	quest.2296CE4418AE62D4.title: "&6ATM奥术师装备&7[ATM Arcanist Gear]&f"
	quest.243008D4DCD789D0.quest_desc: [
		"也可以由野生精魂锻造\\n&7[Can also be forged by Wild Spirits]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_wild.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.243008D4DCD789D0.quest_subtitle: "&a丛林神庙&f&7[Jungle Temples]&f"
	quest.243008D4DCD789D0.title: "Wild &a护甲夹板&f&7[Wild Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.28408BFAA54E4FC6.quest_desc: ["&7&a皮甲&f&r 是你能获得的最差的原版盔甲套装.\\n\\n这主要是因为 &c&lMojang&r 期望你在获得其他盔甲之前先得到它.\\n\\n不过我几乎从未得到过它,因为我很难找到那么多 &8牛&f,抱歉 &c&lMojang&r!\\n&7[Leather Armor is the worst vanilla Armor set you can get. \\n\\nThat is mostly because lMojang expected you to get it before any other. \\n\\nI almost never get it though because I struggle to find that many Cows, sorry lMojang!]&f"]
	quest.28408BFAA54E4FC6.quest_subtitle: "7&7[7]&f"
	quest.28408BFAA54E4FC6.title: "&7&a皮甲&f&7[Leather Armor]&f"
	quest.2A4FE9644F3B9DC1.quest_desc: ["&2一级精华&r 的 &a增强&f 版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of Prudentium.]&f"]
	quest.2A4FE9644F3B9DC1.quest_subtitle: "26&7[26]&f"
	quest.2A4FE9644F3B9DC1.title: "&c三级精华盔甲&7[Tertium Armor]&f"
	quest.2AC0FE608759AD53.quest_desc: ["来自 &e&l机械动力&r 的潜水盔甲不仅提供防护,还赋予多种在水下建造和工作的增益效果.\\n&7[Diving armor from lCreate not only provides armor, but also gives a multitude of buffs for building and working underwater.]&f"]
	quest.2AC0FE608759AD53.quest_subtitle: "7 到 15&7[7 to 15]&f"
	quest.2AC0FE608759AD53.title: "&9潜水盔甲&7[Diving Armor]&f"
	quest.2E0F82F7E1B74033.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l&a元素魔艺&f&r &2大地盔甲&r!\\n\\n&7[lArs Elemental Earth Armor!\\n]&f"
		"它增强 &2大地&r 符文,提高大地和毒系法术的效果.\\n\\n它减少来自 &2大地&r 源的伤害.\\n\\n当穿戴全套时,它还会将部分受到的 &2大地&r 源伤害转化为魔力.\\n&7[It empowers Earth glyphs, increasing the effectiveness of earth and poison-based spells.\\n\\nIt reduces damage from Earth-based sources.\\n\\nIt also converts some incoming Earth-based damage into mana when the full set is worn.]&f"
	]
	quest.2E0F82F7E1B74033.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.2E0F82F7E1B74033.title: "&2大地法师套装&7[Geomancer Outfit]&f"
	quest.2EAA6BE598C83F24.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l&a元素魔艺&f&r &3水盔甲&r!\\n\\n&7[lArs Elemental Water Armor!\\n]&f"
		"这会增强 &3水&r 符文.\\n\\n它减少来自 &3水&r 源的伤害.\\n\\n当穿戴全套时,将部分受到的 &3水&r 源伤害转化为魔力.\\n&7[This boosts Water glyphs.\\n\\nIt reduces damage from Water-based sources.\\n\\nConverts some incoming Water-based damage into mana when the full set is worn.]&f"
	]
	quest.2EAA6BE598C83F24.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.2EAA6BE598C83F24.title: "&3水法师套装&7[Aquamancer Outfit]&f"
	quest.338BD467EBE6EE1F.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从野生唤魔者处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Evokers]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_sentry.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.338BD467EBE6EE1F.quest_subtitle: "&a掠夺者前哨站&f&7[Pillager Outpost]&f"
	quest.338BD467EBE6EE1F.title: "哨兵 &a护甲夹板&f&7[Sentry Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.3403D7502F7BC897.quest_desc: ["字面意义上的无敌,没有什么能击中你并造成伤害.\\n\\n目前你需要用 &e量子 &b升级&r 来升级 &c下界合金盔甲&r,但你在 &6&lATM 团队&r 的朋友们正在努力让那个配方变得更难!\\n\\n而你对此无能为力!&l哇哈哈哈哈哈哈\\n&7[Quite literally invincible, nothing can hit you and do damage. \\n\\nCurrently you need to upgrade Netherite Armor with a Quantum Upgrade but your friends in the lATM Team are working at making that recipe harder! \\n\\nAnd you can't do anything to stop it! lBWAHAHAHAHA]&f"]
	quest.3403D7502F7BC897.quest_subtitle: "无敌&7[Invincible]&f"
	quest.3403D7502F7BC897.title: "&e量子 &b盔甲&r (&l&7MI&r)&7[Quantum Armor (lMI)]&f"
	quest.34D14B807A2DAC0F.quest_desc: ["你以为只有 &5&l&d通用机械&f&r 和 &l&7&d现代工业化&f&r 能玩得开心吗？\\n\\n这套 &5量子盔甲&r 的默认属性与 &c下界合金盔甲&r 相似,但就像 &aMekaSuit&r 一样,它可以使用能量作为护盾.\\n它还有可以安装的升级,让你变得更强大!比如飞行、&a夜视&f,甚至自动充能的能力.\\n\\n但最棒的是它可以 &a链接到&f 你的存储系统!然后,无论你在哪里,都可以自动从中提取能量和任何物品.\\n\\n此外,穿戴全套可以防止 &a辐射&r 杀死你.\\n&7[You think lMekanism and lModern Industrialization can have all the fun? \\n\\nThis Quantum Armor has default stats similar to Netherite Armor but, like the MekaSuit it can use Energy as a shield. \\nIt also has upgrades which can be installed to make you even more powerful! Like Flight, Night Vision, and even the ability to recharge. \\n\\nBut the best part is that it can Linked to your Storage System! Then, you can automatically take Energy out from it and take out any Item from it no matter where you are.\\n\\nFurthermore, wearing the full set can prevent Radiation from killing you.]&f"]
	quest.34D14B807A2DAC0F.quest_subtitle: "你能提供的最大能量&7[As much Energy you can supply]&f"
	quest.34D14B807A2DAC0F.title: "&5量子盔甲&r (&l&bAE2&r)&7[Quantum Armor (lAE2)]&f"
	quest.351159C55159C316.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从被附身的潜影贝处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Shulkers]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_spire.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.351159C55159C316.quest_subtitle: "&a末地城箱子&f&7[End City Chests]&f"
	quest.351159C55159C316.title: "尖塔 &a护甲夹板&f&7[Spire Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.3512F47DADC07EAE.quest_desc: ["&5难以获取盔甲&r,但增强了 &d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r 法术!\\n&7[难得素 Armor but with buffs to lArs Nouveau Spells!]&f"]
	quest.3512F47DADC07EAE.quest_subtitle: "40&7[40]&f"
	quest.3512F47DADC07EAE.title: "&5难以获取奥术师装备&7[难得素 Arcanist Gear]&f"
	quest.3685B52446DEC809.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_gold.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.3685B52446DEC809.title: "&e金&r&7[Gold]&f"
	quest.39796D8EE440F318.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从野生虫群尸壳处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Horde Husks]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_dune.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.39796D8EE440F318.quest_subtitle: "&a沙漠神殿&f&7[Desert Pyramids]&f"
	quest.39796D8EE440F318.title: "Dune &a护甲夹板&f&7[Dune Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.3A840658A11D16A5.quest_desc: ["来自 &7&d气动工艺&f&r 的 &7气动&r 盔甲是一套强大的、终局模块化套装,由你压力网络中的压缩空气驱动.这套盔甲最棒的部分在于它的升级.你可以飞得比量子盔甲还快,跳得极高,并且免受各种伤害.\\n&7[The Pneumatic armor from PneumaticCraft is a powerful, endgame modular suit that runs on compressed air from your pressure network. The best part of this set is its upgrades. You can fly faster than quantum, jump incredibly high, and be safe from all sorts of things.]&f"]
	quest.3A840658A11D16A5.quest_subtitle: "15+&7[15+]&f"
	quest.3A840658A11D16A5.title: "&7&a气动装甲&f&7[Pneumatic Armor]&f"
	quest.3AA836E8EDB52097.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_lapis.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.3AA836E8EDB52097.title: "&9&a青金石&f&r&7[Lapis Lazuli]&f"
	quest.3ABE7074E500494D.quest_desc: ["&7钢&r 用于 &5&l&d通用机械&f&r 中的大多数机器……再加上盔甲,这很不错!\\n&7[Steel is used for most Machines in lMekanism... plus Armor which is nice!]&f"]
	quest.3ABE7074E500494D.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.3ABE7074E500494D.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f&r &7&a钢甲&f&7[lMekanism Steel Armor]&f"
	quest.3AE0198177A8E91B.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从被附身的远古守卫者处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Elder Guardians]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_coast.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.3AE0198177A8E91B.quest_subtitle: "沉船和埋藏的宝藏&7[Shipwrecks and Buried Treasure]&f"
	quest.3AE0198177A8E91B.title: "海岸 &a护甲夹板&f&7[Coast Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.3C662D3A3537F514.quest_desc: ["来自 &6&l&d奥瑞科技&f&r 模组的 Exo 盔甲是一套为实用性和探索而设计的套装,而非战斗.它每件装备都提供很酷的增益,但基础防护非常低.\\n&7[The Exo Armor from the lOritech mod is a set designed for utility and exploration, rather than combat. It offers cool benefits with each piece but provides very little base protection.]&f"]
	quest.3C662D3A3537F514.quest_subtitle: "17&7[17]&f"
	quest.3C662D3A3537F514.title: "&7Exo 头盔&7[Exo Helmet]&f"
	quest.3EA3A6414AB8A39C.quest_desc: [
		"也可以从野生强风处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Strong Breezes]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_flow.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.3EA3A6414AB8A39C.quest_subtitle: "试炼密室&7[Trial Chambers]&f"
	quest.3EA3A6414AB8A39C.title: "Flow &a护甲夹板&f&7[Flow Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.3FCEF8FF45E51608.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_quartz.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.44CC11E67ADD0556.quest_desc: ["来自 &d&l&d禁忌与奥秘&f&r 模组的 &5龙之奥秘&r 盔甲是一套高阶盔甲,提供可观的防护属性.它是该模组 &5黑曜石&r 盔甲的升级版；你需要进入该模组的 &6&a赫菲斯托斯锻炉&f&r 来获取必要的材料.\\n&7[The Draco Arcanus armor from the lForbidden and Arcanus mod is a high-tier set that gives healthy protective stats. It is an upgrade of the mod's Obsidian armor; you need to go into the mod's Hephaestus Forge to acquire the necessary materials.]&f"]
	quest.44CC11E67ADD0556.quest_subtitle: "30&7[30]&f"
	quest.44CC11E67ADD0556.title: "&5龙之奥秘盔甲&7[Draco Arcanus Armor]&f"
	quest.452DC5EB02D592B8.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_amethyst.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.452DC5EB02D592B8.title: "&5紫水晶&r&7[Amethyst]&f"
	quest.4915960FBC94AD0E.quest_desc: ["&7&a压缩铁&f&r 盔甲是一套基础的前期盔甲,是通往模组其他内容的门户.它由皮革盔甲与 &7压缩铁&r 合成,用于介绍如何制造压缩铁.\\n\\n它提供的防护比皮革盔甲略有提升,但等同于铁甲,且弱于钻石甲.\\n&7[Compressed Iron armor is a basic, early-game armor set that functions as a gateway to the rest of the mod. It is crafted from leather armor combined with compressed iron to introduce how to create compressed iron.\\n\\nIt offers a modest increase in protection over leather armor but is equal to iron and weaker than diamond.]&f"]
	quest.4915960FBC94AD0E.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.4915960FBC94AD0E.title: "&7&a压缩铁&f 盔甲&7[Compressed Iron Armor]&f"
	quest.497D222F74A52DF5.quest_desc: ["这才是我喜欢的!铁非常常见,它的盔甲在游戏前期简直不可思议.\\n\\n僵尸和骷髅几乎没有胜算!\\n&7[Now this is what I like! Iron is very common and its Armor is incredible for early game. \\n\\nZombies and Skeletons stand just about no chance!]&f"]
	quest.497D222F74A52DF5.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.49E13245EE169048.quest_desc: ["&6&a防化服&f&r 可能看起来毫无 &a防御&f 价值,但它是防止 &a辐射&r 杀死你的唯一方法(除了 &aMekaSuit 护甲&f 的 &a辐射屏蔽单元&f 和高级 AE 的 &5量子护甲&r).\\n\\n你需要穿戴整套才能防止 &a&a辐射中毒&f&r!\\n\\n&a辐射&r 会杀死附近的其他生物和玩家,玩家可以通过 &6&a防化服&f&r 得救……但生物就没那么幸运了!\\n\\n有关 &a辐射&r 的更多信息,请查看 &5&l&d通用机械&f:反应堆&r 任务页面.\\n&7[The Hazmat Suit might seem useless with no defensive value, but it is the only way of preventing Radiation from killing you (besides the MekaSuit's Radiation Shielding Unit and Advanced AE's Quantum Armor). \\n\\nYou need to wear the entire set to prevent Radiation Poisoning! \\n\\nRadiation will kill other Mobs and Players near it, the Players can be saved with Hazmat Suits... but Mobs aren't so lucky!\\n\\nFor more information about Radiation, check out the lMekanism: Reactors quest page.]&f"]
	quest.49E13245EE169048.quest_subtitle: "0&7[0]&f"
	quest.49E13245EE169048.title: "&6&a防化服&f&7[Hazmat Suit]&f"
	quest.4A9CB8778D37049F.quest_desc: ["你需要使用一次觉醒&a魔法仪式&f来获取物品,以便对&4至高盔甲&r进行另一次觉醒&a魔法仪式&f.\\n\\n我认为这是值得的；这是你能从&2&l神秘农业&r中获得的最佳盔甲!\\n&7[You'll need to use an Awakening Ritual to get the Items to do another Awakening Ritual on Supremium Armor. \\n\\nI think it is worth it; it's the best Armor you can get from lMystical!]&f"]
	quest.4A9CB8778D37049F.quest_subtitle: "36&7[36]&f"
	quest.4A9CB8778D37049F.title: "&6觉醒至高盔甲&7[Awakened Supremium Armor]&f"
	quest.4B9C54DA5CB6D5C9.quest_desc: [
		"也可从野生灾厄蠹虫处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Horde Silverfish]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_host.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4B9C54DA5CB6D5C9.quest_subtitle: "古迹废墟&7[Trail Ruins]&f"
	quest.4B9C54DA5CB6D5C9.title: "Host &a护甲夹板&f&7[Host Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.4C2BB25A757CE834.quest_desc: ["&7橡胶&r盔甲是一套非常前期的防护装备.它主要用作中期科技的合成组件,而非一件正经的装备.&7橡胶&r盔甲提供的防护极少,并非用于&4战斗&r或&2探索&r.\\n&7[Rubber armor is a very early-game set of protection. It is primarily a crafting component for mid-game tech rather than a serious piece of equipment. The rubber armor provides very little protection and is not meant for combat or exploration.]&f"]
	quest.4C2BB25A757CE834.quest_subtitle: "+2&7[+2]&f"
	quest.4C2BB25A757CE834.title: "&8橡胶盔甲&7[Rubber Armor]&f"
	quest.4DF683461225690F.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_iron.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.4DF683461225690F.title: "&7铁&r&7[Iron]&f"
	quest.5064D5F99E2C69C8.quest_desc: ["&9注魔&r的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of Imperium.]&f"]
	quest.5064D5F99E2C69C8.quest_subtitle: "29&7[29]&f"
	quest.5064D5F99E2C69C8.title: "&4至高盔甲&7[Supremium Armor]&f"
	quest.5270883BF008AACE.quest_desc: ["这只是一个关卡,这样我就不必把那么多任务标记为”依赖项已完成”了\\n&7[This is just a gate so I don't have to label so many quests as One Completed with dependencies]&f"]
	quest.5270883BF008AACE.title: "&d神秘学&f 或 &a随机护甲&f 纹饰&7[Occultism OR Random Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.52AFABA08674B6A8.quest_desc: ["&3振金盔甲&r,但强化了&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r法术!\\n&7[振金 Armor but with buffs to lArs Nouveau Spells!]&f"]
	quest.52AFABA08674B6A8.quest_subtitle: "32&7[32]&f"
	quest.52AFABA08674B6A8.title: "&3振金奥术师装备&7[振金 Arcanist Gear]&f"
	quest.52B61FB01D7C12A4.quest_desc: ["&a下级精华&r的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of Inferium.]&f"]
	quest.52B61FB01D7C12A4.quest_subtitle: "23&7[23]&f"
	quest.52B61FB01D7C12A4.title: "&2谨慎盔甲&7[Prudentium Armor]&f"
	quest.537CDA57EBECD176.quest_desc: ["由于身处天空,我们失去了所有盔甲纹饰……那些通常能在各种结构中找到的纹饰都没了.但是,我们有一个解决方案.可靠的老朋友——筛子.用&a金筛网&f筛沙子,有机会获得一个&a随机护甲&f纹饰.\\n&7[We've lost all the armor trims to being in the sky...getting rid of the various structures you normally find them in. But, we have a solution. Good Ol' Sieves. Sieving Sand with a Golden Mesh has a chance to give you a Random Armor Trim.]&f"]
	quest.56975E521D14BDC9.quest_desc: ["&d神秘学&f也提供了从各种附身和野生生物处获取&a护甲纹饰&f的方法.查看&d神秘学&f任务页面和&a魔灵全典&f以&a了解更多信息&f.\\n&7[Occultism also offers a way to get Armor Trims from various Possessed and Wild Mobs. Check the Occultism Quest Page and the Dictionary of Spirits for more information.]&f"]
	quest.56975E521D14BDC9.title: "&a神秘仪式&f&7[Occult Rituals]&f"
	quest.57F3F5875F7CF80C.quest_desc: ["来自&b&l&d戴尔设备&f&r模组的&3苍穹晶&r盔甲是一套三级能量驱动盔甲,提供钻石级别的防护.其酷炫的功能来自你可以安装并用能量驱动的升级模块.\\n&7[The Celestigem armor from the lJust Dire Things mod is a tier-three, energy-powered armor set that offers diamond-level protection. The cool functions come from upgrades that you can install and power with energy.]&f"]
	quest.57F3F5875F7CF80C.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.57F3F5875F7CF80C.title: "&3苍穹晶盔甲&7[Celestigem Armor]&f"
	quest.5865951E4F81C91F.quest_desc: [
		"&7锇&r + &6荧石&r = &e&a强化荧石&f&r!\\n\\n&7[Osmium + Glowstone = Refined Glowstone!\\n]&f"
		"它&7更坚韧&r.\\n&7[It's tougher.]&f"
	]
	quest.5865951E4F81C91F.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.5865951E4F81C91F.title: "&e&a强化荧石&f盔甲&7[Refined Glowstone Armor]&f"
	quest.59771D9B8CAD80C5.quest_desc: ["这可能是你在TTS中获得的&3第一套&r盔甲,因为&7燧石&r相当容易获得.\\n&7[Probably the first armor you're going to get in TTS, as flint is pretty easy to come by.]&f"]
	quest.59771D9B8CAD80C5.quest_subtitle: "12&7[12]&f"
	quest.59771D9B8CAD80C5.title: "&7燧石盔甲&7[Flint Armor]&f"
	quest.5A21B16F7600561A.quest_desc: ["纸板盔甲是个玩笑.它是整个整合包中&3最差&r的盔甲.不过,也许它在潜行方面有些好处……\\n&7[Cardboard Armor is a joke. It is THE worst armor in the entire modpack. Maybe it has some benefits for sneaking around though...]&f"]
	quest.5A21B16F7600561A.quest_subtitle: "4&7[4]&f"
	quest.5A21B16F7600561A.title: "&6纸板盔甲&7[Cardboard Armor]&f"
	quest.5A9C646718EE92C2.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_vibranium.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.5A9C646718EE92C2.title: "&3振金&r&7[振金]&f"
	quest.5C83D5CDD980FD9A.quest_desc: [
		"也可从附身疣猪兽处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Hoglins]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_snout.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5C83D5CDD980FD9A.quest_subtitle: "&a堡垒遗迹&f&7[Bastion Remnants]&f"
	quest.5C83D5CDD980FD9A.title: "猪鼻&a护甲纹饰&f&7[Snout Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.5DDC15AAFD2CAF47.quest_desc: ["&b钻石盔甲&r是&l&2原版&r链条上的下一个,通常也是我们开始附魔的地方!\\n\\n我推荐保护及其各种变种,对于模组物品我们不必太挑剔!\\n&7[Diamond Armor is the next on the lVanilla chain, this is also usually where we start Enchanting it as well! \\n\\nI recommend Protection and its various forms, we don't have to be picky with modded!]&f"]
	quest.5DDC15AAFD2CAF47.quest_subtitle: "20&7[20]&f"
	quest.5DDC15AAFD2CAF47.title: "&b钻石盔甲&7[Diamond Armor]&f"
	quest.5E7CCDE9229A646A.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_allthemodium.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.5E7CCDE9229A646A.title: "&6ATM属&r&7[ATM]&f"
	quest.62161BDE9AAAA4BF.quest_desc: [
		"也可从野生灾厄蠹虫处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Horde Silverfish]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_wayfinder.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.62161BDE9AAAA4BF.quest_subtitle: "古迹废墟&7[Trail Ruins]&f"
	quest.62161BDE9AAAA4BF.title: "寻路者&a护甲纹饰&f&7[Wayfinder Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.65A529C8238E89F1.quest_desc: ["多亏了&5&l&d通用机械&f&r,我们现在可以用&9&a青金石&f&r制作盔甲了!\\n\\n不过它有点烂……\\n&7[Thanks to lMekanism we can now make Armor out of Lapis Lazuli! \\n\\nIt kinda blows though...]&f"]
	quest.65A529C8238E89F1.quest_subtitle: "9&7[9]&f"
	quest.65A529C8238E89F1.title: "&9&a青金石&f盔甲&7[Lapis Lazuli Armor]&f"
	quest.65E733AACBE62EDB.quest_desc: [
		"也可从附身监守者处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Wardens]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_ward.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.65E733AACBE62EDB.quest_subtitle: "远古城市&7[Ancient Cities]&f"
	quest.65E733AACBE62EDB.title: "Ward &a护甲夹板&f&7[Ward Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.66C21934DAFFAC7F.quest_desc: [
		"也可从附身远古守卫者处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Elder Guardians]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_tide.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.66C21934DAFFAC7F.quest_subtitle: "由远古守卫者掉落&7[Dropped from Elder Guardians]&f"
	quest.66C21934DAFFAC7F.title: "Tide &a护甲夹板&f&7[Tide Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.68DABFFB6B3E1A57.quest_desc: [
		"也可从附身末影人处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Endermen]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_eye.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.68DABFFB6B3E1A57.quest_subtitle: "要塞&7[Stronghold]&f"
	quest.68DABFFB6B3E1A57.title: "Eye &a护甲夹板&f&7[Eye Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.6B671CB07D046BEC.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_diamond.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.6B671CB07D046BEC.title: "&b钻石&r&7[Diamond]&f"
	quest.6C5F9D0D447EFB9C.quest_desc: ["你以为我们只有&l&2原版&r吗？\\n\\n&6ATM属盔甲&r拥有更高的&a护甲值&f和&a盔甲韧性&f,外加对魔法的额外防护以及其他增益,你可以在&6&lATM属&r任务页面阅读详情!\\n\\n顺便说一句,你需要&c下界合金&r来合成它.\\n&7[What you think lVanilla was all we got? \\n\\nATM Armor has more Armor Points and Armor Toughness, plus increased Protection against Magic and other buffs you can read about in lATM Quest Page! \\n\\nBTW you will need Netherite to craft it.]&f"]
	quest.6C5F9D0D447EFB9C.quest_subtitle: "24&7[24]&f"
	quest.6C5F9D0D447EFB9C.title: "&6ATM属盔甲&7[ATM Armor]&f"
	quest.6D45C78AD098AF87.quest_desc: ["这是一套高度专业化的盔甲,旨在保护穿戴者免受电气危害,而非用于&4战斗&r防御.它起到”法拉第笼”的作用,使你免疫&7电线&r和&e特斯拉线圈&r的伤害.\\n&7[This is highly specialized armor set designed to protect will from electrical hazards rather than for defense in combat. It functions as a \"Faraday cage,\" giving you immunity to wires and tesla coils. ]&f"]
	quest.6D45C78AD098AF87.quest_subtitle: "7&7[7]&f"
	quest.6D45C78AD098AF87.title: "&7法拉第盔甲&7[Faraday Armor]&f"
	quest.6F76DA3BBAE8337B.quest_desc: ["我们能从&6&lATM属&r获得的最强盔甲,&5难以获得&r!\\n\\n现在拥有100%的&a击退抗性&f和全面提升的属性!\\n\\n同时需要&3振金盔甲&r来制作.\\n&7[The greatest Armor we can get from lATM, 难得素! \\n\\nNow with 100% Knockback Resistance and higher stats everywhere! \\n\\nAlso needs 振金 Armor to make it.]&f"]
	quest.6F76DA3BBAE8337B.quest_subtitle: "40&7[40]&f"
	quest.6F76DA3BBAE8337B.title: "&5难以获得盔甲&7[难得素 Armor]&f"
	quest.71C552678A0F649F.quest_desc: ["&7锇&r生成在深板岩附近,只需要铁镐即可开采,但它的属性比&c下界合金&r还要好!\\n&7[Osmium spawns around Deepslate and only needs Iron to Mine but it gives better stats than Netherite!]&f"]
	quest.71C552678A0F649F.quest_subtitle: "21&7[21]&f"
	quest.71C552678A0F649F.title: "&7锇盔甲&7[Osmium Armor]&f"
	quest.7279700A93E8630B.quest_desc: ["{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_unobtainium.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"]
	quest.7279700A93E8630B.title: "&5难以获得&r&7[难得素]&f"
	quest.729DCB919A92B735.quest_desc: [
		"也可从野生微风处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Wild Breezes]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_bolt.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.729DCB919A92B735.quest_subtitle: "试炼密室&7[Trial Chambers]&f"
	quest.729DCB919A92B735.title: "Bolt &a护甲夹板&f&7[Bolt Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.72DDA413D73E3235.quest_desc: ["&6&lATM属&r盔甲系列的下一个,&3振金&r,在所有属性上都大幅提升!\\n\\n你需要&6ATM属盔甲&r来制作它.\\n&7[Much higher stats in everything with the next in line for lATM Armors, 振金! \\n\\nYou will need ATM Armor to create it.]&f"]
	quest.72DDA413D73E3235.quest_subtitle: "32&7[32]&f"
	quest.72DDA413D73E3235.title: "&3振金盔甲&7[振金 Armor]&f"
	quest.76CDF08465700AA2.quest_desc: [
		"也可从附身监守者处获得\\n&7[Can also be obtained from Possessed Wardens]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basicarmor/armor_silent.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.76CDF08465700AA2.quest_subtitle: "远古城市&7[Ancient Cities]&f"
	quest.76CDF08465700AA2.title: "寂静&a护甲纹饰&f&7[Silence Armor Trim]&f"
	quest.79D3055DE0EEA6B0.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l&a元素魔艺&f&r的&c火焰盔甲&r!\\n\\n&7[lArs Elemental Fire Armor!\\n]&f"
		"这套装备强化&c火焰&r符文,使火系法术更加强大.\\n\\n它提供对&c火焰&r伤害的抗性,穿戴全套时抗性更高.\\n\\n穿戴全套时,它还能将部分受到的&c火焰&r伤害转化为魔力.\\n&7[This set empowers Fire glyphs, making fire-based spells more potent.\\n\\nIt provides resistance to Fire damage, with a higher resistance when the full set is worn.\\n\\nIt also converts some incoming Fire-based damage into mana when the full set is worn.]&f"
	]
	quest.79D3055DE0EEA6B0.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.79D3055DE0EEA6B0.title: "&c纵火者套装&7[Pyromancer Outfit]&f"
	quest.7B500E0577BDFF8F.quest_desc: ["&6青铜&r是&6铜&r和锡的合金.\\n\\n有十几种不同的合金制作方法,我不会告诉你正确的方法.\\n&7[Bronze is a combination of Copper and Tin. \\n\\nThere is a dozen different ways to make the alloy, I won't tell you the right way to do so.]&f"]
	quest.7B500E0577BDFF8F.quest_subtitle: "18&7[18]&f"
	quest.7B500E0577BDFF8F.title: "&6青铜盔甲&7[Bronze Armor]&f"
	quest.7C1D407CF67786F6.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l&a元素魔艺&f&r的&e空气盔甲&r!\\n\\n&7[lArs Elemental Air Armor!\\n]&f"
		"强化&e空气&r符文,这对闪电和诸如跳跃之类的机动性法术很有用.\\n\\n减少来自&e空气&r源的伤害.穿戴全套时,将部分受到的&e空气&r伤害转化为魔力.\\n&7[Empowers Air glyphs, which can be useful for lightning and mobility spells like Leap.\\n\\nReduces damage from Air-based sources.Converts some incoming Air-based damage into mana when the full set is worn.]&f"
	]
	quest.7C1D407CF67786F6.quest_subtitle: "15&7[15]&f"
	quest.7C1D407CF67786F6.title: "&f气动师套装&7[Aethermancer Outfit]&f"
	quest.7F11ABFB2E21B7E4.quest_desc: ["盔甲是&l&2Minecraft&r中非常重要的一部分,它能保护你免受伤害.\\n\\n不同的盔甲部件提供不同的&a护甲值&f.这决定了你盔甲的效果,越多越好!\\n\\n大多数盔甲都可以用&a护甲纹饰&f进行装饰性更改,使用一件盔甲、一个&a护甲纹饰&f和一个用于染色的物品来改变外观!\\n&7[Armor is a very important part of lMinecraft, it is what protects you from harm. \\n\\nDifferent pieces of Armor give different Armor Points. These are what determine the effectiveness for your Armor, the more the merrier!\\n\\nMost armor can be changed for more decoration with Armor Trims, use a piece of Armor with an Armor Trim, and an Item for coloring to change the look!]&f"]
	quest.7F11ABFB2E21B7E4.title: "&l&b基础盔甲&r&7[lBasic Armor]&f"
	quest.7FABB77A60E7962C.quest_desc: ["通过将黑曜石与&b钻石&r融合,我们可以得到&a强化黑曜石粉&f!\\n\\n然后,我们可以将&7锇&r压缩进去,得到锭的形式.\\n\\n之后,我们可以将这些锭制成盔甲,其属性甚至比&6ATM属盔甲&r还要好!\\n&7[By infusing Obsidian with Diamonds we can get Refined Obsidian Dust! \\n\\nThen, we can compress Osmium into it to get it in Ingot form. \\n\\nAfter that, we can turn those Ingots into Armor with better stats than even ATM Armor!]&f"]
	quest.7FABB77A60E7962C.quest_subtitle: "31&7[31]&f"
	quest.7FABB77A60E7962C.title: "&5&a强化黑曜石&f盔甲&7[Refined Obsidian Armor]&f"
	task.27B97C63DC58278E.title: "&a潜水头盔&f&7[Diving Helmets]&f"
	task.337C841AD2B16764.title: "潜水储罐&7[Diving Tanks]&f"
	task.4BDF268861CA744F.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.57895147416291FE.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.597120AD20EEBF1D.title: "&a潜水靴子&f&7[Diving Boots]&f"
	task.73142F195D9B100C.title: "外骨骼胸甲&7[Exo Chestpieces]&f"
	quest.034F2CDF0830254B.quest_desc: [
		"工作原理与物品导入器类似,将&e流体导入器&r放在装有液体的储罐上.然后将&e&a流体接口&f&r放在你想要流体去的地方,并用逻辑电缆连接.最后像之前一样使用变量卡!\\n\\n也能以整数极限的速度抽取流体.\\n\\n不会在世界中放置或移除流体源,它只将流体从一个储罐移动到另一个储罐.\\n&7[Works just like the Item Importer, put the Fluid Importer onto a Tank with Liquid. Then the Fluid Interface on where you want it to go and connect with Logic Cables. Finally Variable Card just like before! \\n\\nAlso can pull Liquids at the Integer Limit. \\n\\nDoes not place or take Fluid Sources from in the world, it only moves Fluids from one Tank to another.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/id_fluid.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.034F2CDF0830254B.title: "&e流体导入&7[Fluid Importing]&f"
	quest.03C40D6A5D722543.quest_desc: ["变量卡是启动诸如导入物品等交互所必需的.你需要将它们放入导入器的其中一个插槽来添加它们.\\n\\n之后,你可以通过+按钮编辑所有内容.你可以更改导入数量、物品槽位、频道,几乎所有设置都可以通过那张卡完成.\\n\\n如果你像我一样只想移动物品,不需要太花哨,就把它放进去,也许可以更改移动数量的限制.\\n&7[Variable Cards are necessary for starting Interactions like Importing Items. You will put them in one of the slots of the Importer to add them. \\n\\nFrom there you can edit everything via the + Button. You can change how much is Importer, which Item Slot, which Channel, practically everything with just that Card. \\n\\nIf you're like me just wanting to move items, nothing too fancy just put it in and maybe change the Limit for how much is moved.]&f"]
	quest.046C417B2ADF3AA7.quest_desc: ["卡片有其限制.物品提取每次操作只能提取8个物品.流体提取只有&a5桶&f.天知道化学和能量的限制是多少.\\n\\n这是模组化的&2&lMinecraft&r,这些限制不够用,我们需要超频它们.\\n\\n在卡片的右上角扔一些超频升级器,就能提升它们可以传输的上限!\\n&7[Cards have their limits. Item Extraction can only extract 8 items per Operation. Fluid Extract at only 5 Buckets. God knows with Chemical and Energy. \\n\\nThis is Modded lMinecraft these limits won't suffice we need to Overclock them. \\n\\nThrow some Overclockers in the top right of the Card and it'll upgrade the cap they can transfer!]&f"]
	quest.046C417B2ADF3AA7.quest_subtitle: "最大:4&7[Max: 4]&f"
	quest.06767BA0AFE8C1EE.quest_desc: ["1... 2... 还有个4在某个地方.\\n\\n要设置一个数字,放入物品后,你可以左键或右键&a点击以切换&f数量.按住Shift键进行相同操作可以以10为单位增减.一旦你设定了数字,就把它放进卡片里!\\n\\n然后它会等待直到有设定数量的物品存在时才开始提取物品.它也会在第一个容器中留下那个数量的物品.\\n&7[1... 2... there's a 4 somewhere as well. \\n\\nTo set a Number put the Item in then you can Left or Right Click to change the amount. Shift and do the same to go by 10s. Once you have a set Number through it into a Card! \\n\\nIt will then wait until that set Number of Items is there to start taking Items. It will also leave that amount in the first Inventory.]&f"]
	quest.0BB562FB44B0AAA7.quest_desc: ["并非只有卡片有限制,所以它们也不是唯一能使用超频升级器的!\\n\\n这些升级器可以放入&c节点&r本身的右下角,提升其执行操作的速度.\\n&7[Cards aren't the only ones with limits, so they also aren't the only ones with Overclockers! \\n\\nThese go into the Node itself on bottom right and boost how fast it does Operations.]&f"]
	quest.0BB562FB44B0AAA7.quest_subtitle: "最大:8&7[Max: 8]&f"
	quest.1834B5C1F8435D7A.quest_desc: [
		"机械管道是&5&l通用机械&f&r让流体流动的方式.\\n\\n&5&l通用机械&f&r中的一些机器需要流体,例如&a电解分离器&f需要水,或者蒸发厂需要水来制造锂.\\n&7[Mechanical Pipes are how lMeka lets the Fluids flow.\\n\\nSome Machines in lMeka will need Fluids like Electrolytic Separator needing Water or Evaporation Plants to make Lithium.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/meka_pipe.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1834B5C1F8435D7A.quest_subtitle: "流体&7[Fluids]&f"
	quest.1C70D739CE464E25.quest_desc: ["工作原理与&2物品卡&r完全相同,你需要提取卡和插入卡.只是这次你是从一个装有&9流体&r的储罐移动到另一个储罐.不,它不会在世界中放置或移除&9流体&r源.\\n&7[Works exactly like the Item Cards, you need Extract and Insert Cards. Just this time you take from Tanks holding Fluids to another Tank. No, it doesn't move Sources of Fluid in or out of the World.]&f"]
	quest.1C70D739CE464E25.title: "&9&a流体卡片&f&7[Fluid Card]&f"
	quest.230582AAFC0A1632.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&eAll Rights Reserved&r许可授权,未经&6AllTheMods Team&r明确许可,此任务不允许在任何非&6AllTheMods Team&r发布的公开整合包中使用.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.2329AA0AFBEF1E13.quest_desc: [
		"&e&lPipez&r是最简单的&f&l物流&r模组.它如此简单,以至于整个模组的内容都能放在这个任务页面里,而且还有空间放更多模组!\\n&7[lPipez is the simplest lLogistics Mod. It's so simple that the entire mod is fit in this Quest Page while having room for more Mods!]&f"
		""
		"将特定的管道连接到你想移动物品的地方,并使用管道扳手来配置哪一侧拉取、推送或不连接.\\n&7[Attach the specific Pipe to where you want to move items and use the Pipe Wrench to configure what side Pulls, Pushes, or doesn't connect.]&f"
		""
		"其他扳手也能与&e&lPipez&r一起使用!\\n&7[Other Wrenches do work with lPipez as well!]&f"
		""
		"(大量使用时可能会造成卡顿,不过仍然没有&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的管道那么卡).\\n&7[(Can be laggy when used in mass, still not as laggy as lMekanism pipes though).]&f"
	]
	quest.2329AA0AFBEF1E13.title: "&l&ePipez 管道&7[lPipez]&f"
	quest.2A6900E87DE8BAE0.quest_desc: ["&a模组过滤器&f 是另一个相当基础的过滤器.你把物品放进去,它同样可以进行白名单或黑名单过滤.但不仅仅是那个物品,而是来自该模组的任何物品.\\n\\n&d神化&f 宝石将只允许 &d神化&f 的物品.&d通用机械&f 合金将只允许 &d通用机械&f 的物品.以此类推.\\n&7[Mod Filter is another pretty basic Filter. This one you put Items in and it will do the same with either Whitelisting or Blacklisting. But instead of only being that Item it will be any Item from that Mod. \\n\\nApotheosis Gem will only allow Apotheosis Items. Mekanism Alloy will only allow Mekanism Items. And so on.]&f"]
	quest.2A976D41F79C34B1.quest_desc: ["&e&lPipez 管道&r 确实有它们自己的物品过滤方式,不过你至少需要一个高级升级才能获得.当放入高级升级后,你可以点击添加按钮来添加过滤器.\\n然后你可以在过滤器中添加:物品、标签或 NBT 数据.\\n\\n在那里你还可以添加设置目的地过滤器.要设置它,请按住 Shift 键 &a右击&f 一个带有该过滤器的容器.\\n\\n你还必须将其设置为白名单过滤器或黑名单过滤器,即只允许过滤器中的物品或除了过滤器之外的所有物品.\\n&7[lPipez do have their own way of Filtering Items, you need atleast an Advanced Upgrade to get it though. When an Advanced Upgrade is in you can click the Add button to add Filters. \\nThen you can add: Item, Tag, or NBT in the Filter. \\n\\nThere you can also add the set Destination Filter. To set it, Shift Right Click an Inventory with it. \\n\\nYou'll also have to set it to either Whitelist the Filter or Blacklist, so only the Filter or everything but the Filter.]&f"]
	quest.2F4458E9921DEB86.quest_desc: [
		"这些&e&l管道&r主要归功于&5&l&d通用机械&f&r.&5&l&d通用机械&f&r以&a气体&r的形式添加了物质的最后一种状态.&a气体&r无法用其他任何&e&l管道&r移动,所以如果你需要移动氢气或&a锂&f,你将需要&a&a气体管道&fz&r.\\n\\n(我总是难以分辨&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的物品是&a气体&r、&b流体&r,还是&a灌注类型&f.当它在机器里时,可能会显示&a气体&r或&b流体&r,这可以帮助你学习.如果不显示,你可以查看JEI中可能涉及它的其他配方!)\\n&7[These lPipez are mostly due to lMekanism. lMekanism adds the last state of matter in the form of Gas. Gas can't be moved with any of the other lPipez so if you need to move Hydrogen or Lithium you'll need Gas Pipez. \\n\\n(I've always had problems telling whether the lMekanism item is Gas, Fluid, or even Infuse Type. When it's in a Machine it might tell Gas or Fluid, which can help teach you. If it doesn't you can check JEI for other recipes that might involve it!)]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/pipez_gas.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.2F4458E9921DEB86.title: "&a&a气体管道&fz&r&7[Gas Pipez]&f"
	quest.3065EA195D0A36BA.quest_desc: ["标签是《我的世界》中分组物品非常重要的一部分.所以我们当然可以利用它来做过滤器!\\n\\n你可以放入一个物品并选择一个标签,或者如果你知道标签,也可以自己输入.\\n\\n这对于像使用工具标签从系统中取出齿轮这样的操作非常有帮助.\\n\\n(你也可以通过输入 /kubejs hand 来查找标签,以了解手中物品的标签.)\\n&7[Tags are very important part of grouping Items in Minecraft. So of course we can take advantage of that for Filters! \\n\\nYou can put an Item in and select a Tag or if you know it, type it in yourself. \\n\\nReally helpful for ones like taking Gear out of a system by using Tag for Tools. \\n\\n(You can also find Tags by doing /kubejs hand to find what's the Tags of the Item in your hand.)]&f"]
	quest.308935C85364B04D.quest_desc: ["每张卡都存储着自己的数据,不断更改每张卡的设置可能会很烦人.所以,我们直接克隆它们吧!\\n\\n用克隆器&a左键点击&f一张卡以复制其数据,然后&a右键点击&f另一张卡以赋予它该数据!\\n&7[With each Card holding their own data it can be pretty annoying constantly changing each Cards settings. So lets just clone them instead! \\n\\nLeft Click a Card with the Cloner to copy its Data, then Right Click a Card to give it that Data!]&f"]
	quest.30DE4F5BC3EDB555.quest_desc: [
		"逻辑传送器是&5&lMeka&r用来远距离移动物品和方块的工具.\\n\\n它们需要被配置为从箱子或抽屉等容器中拉取或推送物品.\\n&7[Logical Transporters are what lMeka uses to move Items and Blocks across distance. \\n\\nThey will need to be Configured to Pull or Push to Inventories like Chests or Drawers.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/meka_transporter.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.30DE4F5BC3EDB555.quest_subtitle: "方块+物品&7[Blocks+Items]&f"
	quest.316B513FE568EF57.quest_desc: [
		"热量是&5&l&d通用机械&f&r中的另一个因素,它为许多机器和多方块结构提供动力.&a热力蒸馏塔&f和&a湮灭反应堆&f都使用热量来工作.而导体就是你用来传输热量的方式!\\n&7[Heat is another factor in lMekanism and it Fuels a lot of Machines and Multiblocks. Thermal Evaporation Plants and Fusion Reactors both use Heat to work. And Conductors is how you will be moving Heat!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/meka_conductor.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.316B513FE568EF57.quest_subtitle: "热量&7[Heat]&f"
	quest.33433A443B65D252.quest_desc: [
		"&b水&r=&b蓝色&r &b水&r=&b流体&r 因此 &b蓝色&r=&b流体&r\\n\\n许多模组都有自己的&b流体&r,甚至《我的世界》本身也有自己的流体,比如&b水&r和&c熔岩&r.你很可能需要移动这些&b流体&r,而一个好方法就是使用&b&a流体传输管道&f&r.\\n\\n这可以连接到无限水源以移动无限的&b水&r!\\n&7[Water=Blue Water=Fluid therefore Blue=Fluid\\n\\nLots of Mods have their own Fluids, with even Minecraft having their own, with Water and Lava. You'll most likely need to move those Fluids and a good way of doing so is with Fluid Pipes. \\n\\nThis can be connected to Sinks to move Infinite Water!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/pipez_fluid.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.33433A443B65D252.title: "&b&a流体传输管道&fz&7[Fluid Pipez]&f"
	quest.34CFE1439262AA72.quest_desc: [
		"&5&l&d通用机械&f&r是一个庞大且受欢迎的科技模组,所以它当然也拥有&l物流&r系统.\\n&7[lMekanism is a huge and popular Tech Mod, so of course it has lLogistics with it.]&f"
		""
		"不同的机器对配置很挑剔,需要在它们的GUI中更改设置才能正确移动物品.然后你可以使用&5&lMeka管道&r来移动任何你需要移动的东西!\\n&7[The different Machines are picky with Configurations and will need to be changed in their GUI to properly move items. Then you can use the lMeka Pipes to move whatever you need to move!]&f"
		""
		"但是等等,它们不仅仅适用于&5&l&d通用机械&f&r!它们也适用于许多其他机器!只需要用扳手配置为推送和拉取即可.\\n&7[But wait it's not just lMekanism these work for! They work for plenty of other machines as well! Just need to be Configured with a Wrench to Push and Pull.]&f"
		""
		"(大量使用时可能会造成一些卡顿,所以要小心使用它们).\\n&7[(These can cause a bit of lag when used in mass so be careful with them).]&f"
	]
	quest.34CFE1439262AA72.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f&7[lMekanism]&f"
	quest.36836AD948F96B9F.quest_desc: [
		"&a简易&f的&e&l管道&r,&e物品管道&r.\\n\\n它会将物品从一个容器移动到另一个容器.可以是从一个箱子到另一个箱子,从农场到系统,甚至从采石场到熔炉.\\n\\n非常简单,只需将&e管道&r连接到你想移动的物品来源,然后用扳手配置它从哪一侧拉取物品.\\n&7[The simplest of the simplest of lPipes, the Item Pipe. \\n\\nIt will move Items from one Inventory to another. Could be from one Chest to another, could be a Farm to a System, or even a Quarry to a Smelter. \\n\\nVery simple just connect the Pipes to what you want moved, and use your Wrench to configure which side it Pulls from. ]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/pipez_item.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.36836AD948F96B9F.title: "&e物品管道&7[Item Pipez]&f"
	quest.47768B1FFD57D56E.quest_desc: ["你是不是很讨厌&4红石&r必须布线到各处？既然我们可以有无线FE,为什么不能有无线&4红石&r？多亏了&c&lLaserIO&r,我们终于可以实现了.你可以用&4卡&r输入一个&4&a红石信号&f&r,然后使用&4输出卡&r在别处输出&4信号&r!\\n&7[Don't you just hate Redstone having to be wired to everywhere? If we can have Wireless FE why not Wireless Redstone? Finally we can thanks to lLaserIO. You can Input a Redstone Signal with the Card then use an Output Card to Output the Signal somewhere else!]&f"]
	quest.47768B1FFD57D56E.title: "&4&a红石卡&f&7[Redstone Card]&f"
	quest.47A2BEFB11F4D581.quest_desc: ["基础过滤器非常……容易使用!只需将物品放入其中,它们现在就被过滤了.\\n\\n你可以更改设置,使其要么白名单/仅允许那些物品,要么黑名单/仅拒绝那些物品.\\n\\n你还可以设置是否匹配&aNBT数据&f.匹配&aNBT数据&f意味着拥有相同的附魔、耐久度,甚至是物品内部的生物.如果选择不匹配,它将处理任何该物品,无论NBT如何.\\n&7[The Basic Filter is pretty... easy to use! Simply put Items into it and they are now filtered. \\n\\nYou can change it so it either Whitelists/allows only those Items or that is Blacklists/denies only those Items. \\n\\nYou can also have it so it either matches NBT data or not. Matching NBT Data would mean having same Enchantments, Durabilitiy, or even Mobs inside of whatever Item. If selected to not match it will do any of that Item regardless of NBT.]&f"]
	quest.493D04D954E4FBA0.quest_desc: [
		"&5&l&d通用机械&f&r是科技模组……你为什么惊讶它的机器需要能量？\\n&7[lMekanism is Tech Mod... why are you surprised it needs Energy for its Machines?]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/meka_cable.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.493D04D954E4FBA0.quest_subtitle: "能量&7[Energy]&f"
	quest.4BC2D7FCDD792DBA.quest_desc: [
		"因为普通的&2&l我的世界&r物品、方块和流体还不够.增加的热量和能量也不够.\\n\\n&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的其余部分是通过加压管道移动的.气体是主要部分,因为如果你使用&5&l&d通用机械&f&r,你将使用像氢气和氧气这样的气体.\\n&a灌注类型&f类似,比如煤炭灌注和红石灌注.浆液用于矿石处理.\\n染料颜料是颜色的本质,任何染色的物品都可以通过&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的那部分来改变.\\n&7[Because the normal lMinecraft Items, Blocks, and Fluids wasn't enough. And the added Heat and Energy wasn't either. \\n\\nThe rest of lMekanism is moved with Pressurized Tubes. Gases are the main ones as if you're using lMekanism you will be using Gases like Hydrogen and Oxygen. \\nInfuse Types are similar like Coal Infuse and Redstone Infuse. Slurries are used with Ore Processing. \\nAnd Dye Pigments are the essence of Color, any item that is Dyed can be changed with that part of lMekanism.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/meka_tube.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4BC2D7FCDD792DBA.quest_subtitle: "气体+更多&7[Gas+More]&f"
	quest.4C41FD926F31180B.quest_desc: ["为了用&c&lLaserIO&r移动&2物品&r,你需要一些&2物品卡&r.\\n\\n将一张设置为提取并放在&c&a激光节点&f&r你想要导入的那一侧.然后将另一张设置为插入并放在你想要物品导出到的那一侧.\\n\\n如果存在多个提取位置,你可以更改提取卡的多个设置,以决定物品的去向顺序.&a轮询&f将使其按顺序提取物品,而不是优先最近的容器.\\n&7[In order to move Items with lLaserIO you'll need some Item Cards. \\n\\nSet one to Extract and put it on the side of the Laser Node you want to Import from. Then set the other to Insert and put it to the side you want the Items to Export to. \\n\\nThere are multiple settings you can change with the Extract in order of where you want the Items to go if there's multiple places to Extract from. Round Robin will make it Extract items in an order instead of closest Inventory first.]&f"]
	quest.4C41FD926F31180B.title: "&2物品卡&7[Item Card]&f"
	quest.4FBAB3A0FBF8CE2F.quest_desc: [
		"既然可以移动所有东西,何必担心移动的是什么!&5&a通用管道&fz&r甚至比&c&a能量管道&fz&r更不挑剔.它们可以移动&e物品&r、&b流体&r或&c能量&r.\\n&7[Why worry about what's being moved when you can just move everything! Universal Pipez are even less discriminatory than Energy Pipez. They can move Items, Fluids, or Energy. ]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/pipez_universal.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4FBAB3A0FBF8CE2F.title: "&5&a通用管道&fz&7[Universal Pipez]&f"
	quest.52F85CED20C8B1E9.quest_desc: ["&e能量&r必须以某种方式传输,最好是我们希望它去的地方.像移动&2物品&r、&9流体&r和&5化学品&r一样移动它!\\n&7[Energy has to get around somehow, preferably where we want it to go. Move it around just the same as with Items, Fluids, and Chemicals!]&f"]
	quest.52F85CED20C8B1E9.title: "&e&a能量卡&f&7[Energy Card]&f"
	quest.53EC96FA0E7C4ED4.quest_desc: [
		"每个科技模组都需要&c能量&r,无论是FE、RF还是其他什么!&c&a能量管道&fz&r不挑剔,它只管移动!\\n\\n有些机器有严格的&c能量&r输入输出端口,所以一定要检查那些!\\n&7[Every Tech Mod needs Energy, whether it's FE, RF or something else! Energy Pipez don't discriminate, it just moves! \\n\\nSome Machines have strict IO ports for Energy so make sure to check for those!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/pipez_energy.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.53EC96FA0E7C4ED4.title: "&c&a能量管道&fz&7[Energy Pipez]&f"
	quest.5C0F6B1C93A52113.quest_desc: ["现在,这才是&c&lLaserIO&r真正的心脏!&c&a激光节点&f&r是实际放置卡片以使其工作的地方.\\n\\n它们将从四个基本方向以及上下方向的相邻容器中移动物品.为了移动到更远的容器,你需要第二个&c节点&r,并用扳手通过Shift &a右键点击&f第一个节点,然后&a右键点击&f第二个节点来连接它们.\\n\\n你将卡片放入正确方向的插槽中,也可以在那里放入&a节点超频器&f以使其工作更快.\\n&7[Now this is the true Heart of lLaserIO! The Laser Nodes are where the actual Cards will go into in order to work. \\n\\nThey will move Items from any adjacent Inventory in the 4 Cardinal Directions and Up and Down. In order to move to Farther Inventories you'll need a second Node and Connect them with the Wrench by Shift Right Clicking 1 and Right Clicking the 2nd. \\n\\nYou'll put the Cards into the Slots of the correct Direction and you can put Node Overclockers there as well to make it work faster. ]&f"]
	quest.5F1218CF8EFC607B.quest_desc: [
		"&c&lLaserIO&r是DireWolf对&a&l&d末影接口&f&r的&l物流&r系统的延续.\\n&7[lLaserIO is DireWolf's continuation of lEnderIO's lLogistics.]&f"
		""
		"这一切都是关于通过&c激光&r移动物品!谁不爱&c激光&r呢？!\\n&7[It's all about moving items via Lasers! Who doesn't love Lasers?!]&f"
		""
		"而这一切都始于&a逻辑芯片&f.\\n&7[And it all starts with the Logic Chip.]&f"
	]
	quest.5F1218CF8EFC607B.title: "&c&lLaser IO 激光输入输出&7[lLaser IO]&f"
	quest.6112956E19017D2D.quest_desc: ["逻辑电缆与其他&e&l管道&r或&5&lMeka管道&r不同.其他管道充当漏斗,物品从一个容器移动到管道,然后进入第二个容器.逻辑电缆直接跳过了中间环节,这也跳过了很多卡顿.\\n\\n它们仅用于连接导入器和接口.\\n&7[Logic Cables are different from other lPipez or lMeka pipes. The other Pipes act as hoppers, the items move from 1 Inventory, into the Pipe, then into the 2nd Inventory. Logic Cables just skip the middle man which also skips a lotta lag. \\n\\nThey are just for connecting Importers and Interfaces.]&f"]
	quest.617695A9CA45D88F.quest_desc: ["当使用&c&lLaserIO&r进行&l物流&r时,你最终可能会有很多卡片.每张卡片都会占用你物品栏的一个格子,可能会变得相当拥挤.我希望它们有一个存放卡片的地方……哦,等等,它们有,那就是&a物流卡暂存器&f!\\n\\n你可以在其中存放多张卡片,当你打开一个&a激光节点&f时,&a物流卡暂存器&f也会像第二个物品栏一样打开.非常有用!\\n&7[When using lLaserIO for lLogistics you might end up with MANY Cards. With each taking a slot in your Inventory it can get pretty crampt. I wish they had a storage for Cards... oh wait they do, it's the Card Holder! \\n\\nYou can store multiple Cards in it and when you open a Laser Node the Card Holder will open up as well like a second Inventory. Very helpful!]&f"]
	quest.6718043D0F2D1830.quest_desc: ["DireWolf被要求为他的卡片添加功能,以使其与&5&l&d通用机械&f&r及其……其他物质状态一起工作.加压管道可以移动的一切,这些卡片都可以.气体、&a灌注类型&f和颜料.\\n&7[DireWolf was asked to make an addition of his Cards to work with lMekanism and its... other states of matter. Everything Pressurized Tubes can move, these cards can. Gas, Infuse Types, and Pigments.]&f"]
	quest.6718043D0F2D1830.title: "&5化学品卡&7[Chemical Card]&f"
	quest.67A0164D3A25BE73.quest_desc: ["曾经想在方块之间安装管道吗？让我向你介绍&3传输标签&r.&3传输标签&r可用于物品和流体.\\n\\n&l如何使用&r\\n\\n你可以通过潜行&a右键点击&f方块来将&3标签&r放置在方块上.\\n你可以通过手持另一个&3标签&r或一个&#FFAC3B标签访问器&r并&a右键点击&f已放置的&3标签&r来与之交互.\\n你可以通过手持另一个&3标签&r或一个&#FFAC3B标签访问器&r并左键点击&3标签&r来移除已放置的&3标签&r.\\n你可以使用&#FFAC3B标签访问器&r透过方块访问&3标签&r.\\n\\n&l加速&r\\n\\n你可以通过在数量或速度槽中添加相同类型的&3标签&r来加速&3标签&r.\\n&7[Ever wanted to fit a pipe between blocks? Allow me to introduce you to Transfer Labels. Transfer Labels can be used for items and fluids.\\n\\nlHow to use\\n\\nYou can place Labels on blocks by sneak right clicking onto blocks.\\nYou can interact with the Label by holding another Label or a &#FFAC3BLabel Accessor and right clicking the placed Label.\\nYou can remove the placed Label by left clicking the Label while holding another Label or a &#FFAC3BLabel Accessor.\\nYou can access Labels through blocks using the &#FFAC3BLabel Accessor.\\n\\nlAcceleration\\n\\nYou can accelerate the Labels by adding the same type of Label in the amount or speed slots.]&f"]
	quest.67A0164D3A25BE73.quest_subtitle: "当你的方块之间需要安装管道时&7[When you gotta fit a pipe between your blocks]&f"
	quest.67A0164D3A25BE73.title: "传输标签&7[Transfer Labels]&f"
	quest.6A962535CD68713E.quest_desc: ["&e&l管道&r移动更多!\\n\\n所有升级都会增加&e&l管道&r的移动量,并赋予更多与&e&l管道&r一起使用的选项.\\n\\n基础升级允许&e&l管道&r使用红石激活,可以更改分发方式:最近优先、最远优先、轮询或随机,并可以添加过滤器.\\n\\n改进、高级和终极升级不会提供任何新功能,它们只是移动得更多!\\n&7[lPipez move more! \\n\\nAll Upgrades increase the amount the lPipez move and also grant more options to use with the lPipe. \\n\\nBasic Upgrade allows Redstone Activation with lPipez, to change distribution either:Closest First, Farthest First, Round-Robin, or Random, and to add Filters.\\n\\nImproved, Advanced, and Ultimate upgrades don't grant anything new they just move more!]&f"]
	quest.6CD7D99AA102A5C3.quest_desc: ["&n&f&l物流&r:\\n一个移动、管理和存储物品或资源的系统.\\n\\n在模组《我的世界》中,这几乎是相同的,移动物品!有了模组,你将需要物品,而且是成千上万的,天哪,如果你想要&6&l星&r,那将达到数百万!所以你需要将物品从工厂、机器、农场,尤其是箱子中移动出来.这就是&l&f物流&r的用途.\\n&7[lLogistics: \\nA system of moving, managing, and storing items or resources. \\n\\nIn Modded Minecraft it's quite the same, moving items! With Modded you will need items and by the thousands, heck if you want the lStar it gets in the millions! So you'll need to move items from factories, machines, farms, and especially chests. That's what lLogistics is for.]&f"]
	quest.6CD7D99AA102A5C3.title: "&l物流&7[lLogistics]&f"
	quest.6E05B62A40D5A891.quest_desc: [
		"&3&l&d动态联合/集成动力&f&r全是关于&f&l物流&r的!它几乎是&l物流&r的定义.\\n&7[lIntegrated Dynamics is all about lLogistics! It's practically the definition of lLogistic.]&f"
		""
		"它全是关于移动、管理和存储物品的.天哪,你甚至可能不需要扳手,它设计得太好了!不过还是备一个以防万一.\\n&7[It's all about moving, managing, and storing items. Heck you might not even need the Wrench for it, it's so well designed! Get one just incase though.]&f"
		""
		"(卡顿最少的管道解决方案,推荐使用这些).\\n&7[(Least laggy pipe solution, these are recommended).]&f"
	]
	quest.6E05B62A40D5A891.title: "&3&l&d动态联合/集成动力&f&7[lIntegrated Dynamics]&f"
	quest.6F152402756DA35E.quest_desc: [
		"要使它工作,将物品导入器放在你想要拉取物品的容器上.接下来,将接口放在第二个容器上,并用逻辑电缆连接它们.然后,将变量卡放入导入器并按你的意愿更改它.\\n\\n它可以被更改为以整数限制(超过20亿)导入物品.\\n&7[To get this working put the Item Importer onto the Inventory you want Items pulled from. Next, put the Interface on the second Inventory and connect them with Logic Cables. Then, put in the Variable Card into the Importer and change it as you please. \\n\\nIt can be changed to Import Items at the Integer Limit (Over 2 Billion).]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/id_item.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6F152402756DA35E.title: "&f物品导入&7[Item Importing]&f"
	quest.76CECFB244F39F18.quest_desc: [
		"只需将一个&3能量导入器&r拍到一个&a移动能源&f上,并用逻辑电缆将其连接到一个&3&a能量接口&f&r!放入并编辑变量卡,你就能像专业人士一样移动能量了!\\n\\n我不得不说,我发现它在导入或导出到&a通量接入点&f和点时存在问题,所以请注意这一点.\\n&7[Just smack an Energy Importer onto a Power Source and connect it to an Energy Interface with Logic Cables! Put and edit the Variable Cards and you'll be moving Power like a pro! \\n\\nI do have to say I found it having problems with Importing or Exporting to Flux Plugs and Points so be mindful of that.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/id_energy.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.76CECFB244F39F18.title: "&3能量导入&7[Energy Importing]&f"
	quest.7AD6E01ED01E6F13.quest_desc: ["这些是一些最快、最易用、最多功能的物品和流体传输设备.使用荧石将传输速度增加到每刻堆/桶,钻石允许你专注于发送到指定方块的特定MB或物品数量(输出瞬移器上放荧石,输入瞬移器上放钻石粒).\\n&7[These are some of the fastest, easiest to use, and most versatile item and fluid transfer devices there are. Use Glowstone to increase transfers to stacks/buckets per tick, and diamonds allow you to focus a specific MB or item amount being sent into the specified block (glowstone on output translocator, diamond nugget on input translocator).]&f"]
	quest.7AD6E01ED01E6F13.quest_subtitle: "又回来了……&7[Back again...]&f"
	quest.7AD6E01ED01E6F13.title: "猜猜谁回来了？&7[Guess who's back?]&f"
	quest.7BC8F50A89A3BE1A.quest_desc: ["这些仅用于连接&c&a激光节点&f&r彼此以及连接到连接器.不太重要,我只是想保持扳手的主题.\\n\\n它确实可以作为其他配置的扳手使用!\\n&7[These are just used to Connect Laser Nodes to each other and to Connectors. Not too important I just wanted to keep with the theme of Wrenches. \\n\\nIt does work as a Wrench for other Configs!]&f"]
	quest.7EE27C3908008E20.quest_desc: ["如果你需要将&c&a激光节点&f&r远距离连接,试试使用连接器!像平常一样使用扳手即可.\\n&7[If you need to string your Laser Nodes a far distance try using Connectors! Just use the Wrench like normal.]&f"]
	task.1807A230BA87899B.title: "传输标签&7[Transfer Labels]&f"
	task.2BA7FC10243AA011.title: "加压管道&7[Pressurized Tubes]&f"
	task.337725ECA2C04090.title: "逻辑传送器&7[Logical Transporters]&f"
	task.4448DE84ABA737BE.title: "通用电缆&7[Universal Cables]&f"
	task.48A30B08A090BD75.title: "扳手&7[Wrenches]&f"
	task.48CF7A7622423DEA.title: "管道升级&7[Pipe Upgrades]&f"
	task.4CCB830CFDD43B5E.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.5B7926B511000F1F.title: "机械管道&7[Mechanical Pipes]&f"
	task.5E4B74F97BDED243.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.77187686AC2440DB.title: "瞬移器&7[Translocators]&f"
	task.79E961F671475850.title: "热力学导体&7[Thermodynamic Conductors]&f"
	quest.0A0C5A2F8DDED257.quest_desc: ["&e戴森立方体&r是终极能源,能产生高达惊人的&l&a1 GFE/t&r&r!\\n\\n设置一个&e电磁轨道弹射控制器&r,将&b太阳帆&r和&b光束&r发射到环绕太阳的轨道上.你可以通过其底面的中心&b自动&r输入物品(你绝对需要自动化才能达到最大功率输出).不幸的是,它在&o正午、夜晚或下雨时无法发射&r.\\n\\n为了收集那辉煌的能量,建造一个&b射线接收控制器&r.它从其底面的中心输出能量,但在&e夜晚&r或&e下雨&r时&o无法接收能量&r.\\n\\n你可以将光束和太阳帆&e打包&r成捆以加快发射速度,这比一个一个发送要容易得多.\\n\\n为了达到最大输出,你需要向轨道发送&c8,333,333&r个光束和&c49,999,998&r个太阳帆,这数量相当庞大.\\n\\n在你开始扩展到那个规模之前,请确保你已经建立了一些&a强大的资源生成&r设施.\\n&7[The Dyson Cube is the ultimate power source, producing up to an insane l1GFE/t!\\n\\nSet up an EM Rail Ejector Controller to launch Solar Sails and Beams into orbit around the Sun. You can input items automatically through the center of the bottom face (you'll definitely need automation to reach maximum power output). Unfortunately, it cannot fire at midday, at night, or during rain.\\n\\nTo collect that glorious energy, build a Ray Receiver Controller. It outputs power from the center of its bottom face but cannot receive power during night or rain.\\n\\nYou can package beams and sails into bundles for faster launches, which is much easier than sending them one by one.\\n\\nFor maximum output, you'll need to send 8,333,333 beams and 49,999,998 sails into orbit, which is quite a lot.\\n\\nBefore you start scaling up to that level, make sure you've got some robust resource generation in place.]&f"]
	quest.0A0C5A2F8DDED257.quest_subtitle: "太阳之力,尽在掌握&7[The power of the Sun, in the palm of your hand]&f"
	quest.0A0C5A2F8DDED257.title: "&e戴森立方体&7[Dyson Cube]&f"
	quest.0BB42C5861B22D32.quest_desc: ["&b&a菌丝网络产能反应堆&f&r由所有菌丝发电机在反应堆方块附近同时工作组成,总共产生&a25 MFE/t&r.\\n\\n听起来都不错,但你需要自动化一些东西才能让它工作,看看每个菌丝发电机需要消耗什么来工作,并将其自动化.大多数东西很简单,但其他的就没那么简单了……&o说的就是祛魔菌丝发电机&r.\\n\\n但当你把所有东西都自动化之后,你不必只停留在一个反应堆,你可以制造更多.\\n&7[The Mycelial Reactor consists of all the Mycelial Generators working at the same time, near the reactor block, and it produces a total of 25MFE/t.\\n\\nAll sounds good, but you need to automate some stuff to get it working, see what each Mycelial Generator consumes to work, and automate it, most things are simple, but others, not that much... looking at Disenchanting Mycelial Generator.\\n\\nBut after you get it all automated, you don't need to stop at one, you can make more reactors.]&f"]
	quest.0BB42C5861B22D32.quest_subtitle: "这不是你的菌丝反应堆&7[It's not Yourcelial Reactor]&f"
	quest.0BB42C5861B22D32.title: "&9&d工业先锋&f: &b&a菌丝网络产能反应堆&f&7[Industrial Foregoing: Mycelial Reactor]&f"
	quest.11D09E918015355C.quest_desc: ["&d通用机械&f的&c&a热力发电机&f&r是基础发电的另一种方式.它有两种发电模式:\\n\\n&9被动模式:&r用熔岩源方块或流动方块包围发电机,会随着时间的推移通过热量产生被动能量.在顶部放置一个熔岩源方块,让它从侧面流下.确保先连接管道来传输能量!\\n\\n&9主动模式:&r将可燃材料如煤炭或木头放入发电机中,燃料会燃烧产生能量.这种方式效率不高.\\n&7[Mekanism's Heat Generator is a different take on basic power production. It has two modes of creating power:\\n\\nPassive: Surrounding the generator with Lava source or flowing blocks creates passive power over time through heat. Place one Lava source block on top and let it flow over the sides. Make sure to have Pipes connected for energy first!\\n\\nActive: Placing combustible materials such as Coal or Wood into the generator will burn the fuel to create power. This is not very efficient.]&f"]
	quest.11D09E918015355C.title: "&c&a热力发电机&f&7[Heat Generator]&f"
	quest.1409C17773B6A131.quest_desc: ["所有升级都会增加&e&lPipez&r的传输量,并提供更多与&e&l管道&r一起使用的选项.\\n\\n基础升级允许使用红石激活&e&lPipez&r,以更改分配方式:最近优先、最远优先、轮询或随机,并可以添加过滤器.\\n\\n改进、高级和终极升级不会提供任何新功能,它们只是传输得更多!\\n&7[All Upgrades increase the amount the lPipez move and also grant more options to use with the lPipe. \\n\\nBasic Upgrade allows Redstone Activation with lPipez, to change distribution either:Closest First, Farthest First, Round-Robin, or Random, and to add Filters.\\n\\nImproved, Advanced, and Ultimate upgrades don't grant anything new they just move more!]&f"]
	quest.1409C17773B6A131.title: "&9Pipez:&a升级&7[Pipez: Upgrades]&f"
	quest.1BE26A00A420DAE3.quest_desc: ["在这个模组中,你需要&a&a通量核心&f&r和&a通量方块&r来制作网络的核心部件.每样都做一些!\\n&7[In this mod, you'll need Flux Cores and Flux Blocks to craft the core parts of your network. Make a few of each!]&f"]
	quest.1BE26A00A420DAE3.quest_subtitle: "核心所需之物&7[Of Cores you need these]&f"
	quest.1BE26A00A420DAE3.title: "”核心”合成材料&7[The \"Core\" Crafting Materials]&f"
	quest.1F81EA5E45424308.quest_desc: ["如果你在寻找从机器中获取能量的不同方式,这里可以找到!\\n\\n有几种传输能量的选项,包括&a有线&r和&9无线&r.\\n&7[If you're looking for different ways to get power out of your machines, this is where you can find it!\\n\\nThere are several options, both wired and wireless, for transferring power.]&f"]
	quest.1F81EA5E45424308.title: "&f&l传输能量&7[lTransferring Power]&f"
	quest.27A4FA38992448A0.quest_desc: [
		"&d通量网络&f也提供了一种无线为物品充电的方式,甚至可以跨维度!\\n\\n一旦你将一个接入点连接到你的能源系统,你会想要制作&9&a通量控制器&f&r并将其放置下来.\\n\\n右键点击它以打开界面,然后进入”无线充电”标签页.在那里,你可以选择你想要保持充电状态的物品栏的每个部分.要激活,请确保点击底部的切换按钮以启用无线充电,然后点击应用!\\n\\n&7[Flux Networks also provides a way to charge your items wirelessly, even across dimensions!\\n\\nOnce you have a Plug attached to your power system, you'll want to make the Flux Controller and place it down.\\n\\nRight-click on it to bring up the interface, and go to the \"Wireless Charging\" tab. From there, you can select each section of your inventory you'd like to keep charged. To activate, make sure to hit the toggle button at the bottom to enable Wireless Charging, then click apply!\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basic_power/wireless_ui.png width:125 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.27A4FA38992448A0.title: "无线充电&7[Wireless Charging]&f"
	quest.2EB7784D5296F410.quest_desc: [
		"&a右键点击&f一个功能正常的通量网络方块会给你这个界面.\\n\\n每个接入点或接出点都可以被命名,拥有自定义的优先级,以及自定义的能量传输限制.这允许你完全控制系统中的所有部分.\\n\\n&a绕过限制&r会忽略设定的限制.\\n\\n还有其他几个标签页可以查看,主要是关于你网络的统计数据!\\n\\n&7[Right clicking a functional Flux Network block will give you this UI.\\n\\nEach Plug or Point can be named, have a custom priority level, and have a custom power transfer limit. This allows complete control over all parts of your system.\\n\\nBypass Limit ignores the limit set.\\n\\nThere are several other tabs to check out, mostly for statistics on your network!\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/basic_power/flux_ui.png width:125 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.35ABB0DEE70DF7FD.quest_desc: ["信不信由你,&aPowah&r模组有一些获取……能量的绝佳选择.\\n\\n一定要查看&cPowah&r任务章节了解更多!\\n&7[Believe it or not, the Powah mod has some great options for getting...power.\\n\\nMake sure to check out the Powah quest chapter to learn more!]&f"]
	quest.35ABB0DEE70DF7FD.title: "更多&aPowah&r!&7[More Powah!]&f"
	quest.35CC898E0E49FE58.quest_desc: ["&9&d通量网络&f&r是一个旨在满足你所有无线能量需求的模组.\\n\\n该模组本身没有发电的方式,但它可以存储和无线传输能量,甚至可以跨维度.它甚至可以为物品栏中的物品充电.\\n\\n使用这个模组,你甚至可以在飞行时为你的喷气背包充电.\\n\\n要开始使用这个模组,你需要一些通量粉尘.合成一些&a黑曜石1x&f压缩(在工作台中用9个黑曜石合成),放置它,然后在它上面扔一些红石.在漂浮的红石正上方(上方一格)放置一些黑曜石,然后左键点击(击打)黑曜石.\\n&7[Flux Networks is a mod that aims to be the solution to all of your wireless power needs.\\n\\nThe mod itself does not have a way to generate power, but it can store and wirelessly transmit power, even across dimensions. It can even charge your items in your inventory.\\n\\nYou can even charge your Jetpacks while you are flying with this mod.\\n\\nTo get started with the mod, you'll need some Flux Dust. Craft some Obsidian 1x Compressed (9 Obsidian in crafting table), place it down, then throw some Redstone on top of it. Place some Obsidian right above the floating Redstone (1 block above), then left click (punch) the Obsidian.]&f"]
	quest.35CC898E0E49FE58.quest_subtitle: "终极无线能源解决方案&7[The Ultimate Wireless Power Solution]&f"
	quest.35CC898E0E49FE58.title: "&8&d通量网络&f&7[Flux Networks]&f"
	quest.36DEA17CBB696CC7.quest_desc: ["如果你右键点击接入点,你会看到通量网络界面.在右上角最远处,点击+按钮来创建你的第一个网络.你需要设置一个密码来创建网络,但你也可以设置一个颜色!\\n\\n从这里,你可以进入&a网络选择&f标签页,在接入点上激活你的网络.如果接入点连接到了能源,你现在可以使用&a通量接出点&f在你系统的任何地方利用那个能量!\\n\\n专业提示:如果你想用不同的能源为系统的不同部分供电,你可以创建多个网络!\\n&7[If you right-click on the Plug, you'll see the Flux Network UI. On the far top-right corner, click on the + button to create your first network. You'll need to set a password to create the network, but you can also set a color!\\n\\nFrom here, you can go to the Network Selection tab to activate your network on the Plug. If the Plug is attached to a power source, you can now harness that power anywhere in your system using a Flux Point!\\n\\nPro Tip: You can create multiple networks if you want to have different power sources powering different parts of your systems!]&f"]
	quest.36DEA17CBB696CC7.quest_subtitle: "成为网络管理员!&7[Becoming a Network Admin!]&f"
	quest.3B3E12581F9F0482.quest_desc: [
		"&b&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f&r添加了一个称为&d&a能量核心&f&r的多方块结构.\\n\\n虽然它可能看起来令人困惑,但最终等级可以存储&m9,223,372,036,854,775,808 FE&r,基本上是无限能量.\\n\\n更多信息,请查看&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f章节!\\n&7[Draconic Evolution adds a multiblock called the Energy Core.\\n\\nWhile it may seem confusing, the final tier can hold 9,223,372,036,854,775,808 FE basically infinite power.\\n\\nFor more information, check out the Draconic Evolution Chapter!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_8on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.3B3E12581F9F0482.quest_subtitle: "基本上是无限存储&7[Basically Infinite Storage]&f"
	quest.3B3E12581F9F0482.title: "&9&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f: &d&a能量核心&f&7[Draconic Evolution: Energy Core]&f"
	quest.3BDB94F17765EE77.quest_desc: ["如果你想产生大量能量,你可以从扩大&9中期能源&r部分的一些选项开始.让你的&a反应堆&r变得更大.将你的&9&a热力发电机&f&r升级到硝基级.尽情发挥吧.\\n\\n然而,你可能需要更多的能量.\\n&7[If you're looking to generate a ton of power, you can start by scaling up some of the options from the Mid Game Power section. Make your Reactors bigger. Upgrade your Thermo Generators to Nitro. Go wild.\\n\\nHowever, you may need even more power.]&f"]
	quest.3BDB94F17765EE77.quest_subtitle: "超出你所需的能量&7[More Power Than You'll Need]&f"
	quest.3BDB94F17765EE77.title: "终局能源选项&7[End Game Power Options]&f"
	quest.42D173B9FF8D16E4.quest_desc: ["在寻找游戏早期的能源选项吗？这些是让你开始发电的好方法.\\n\\n这些不会产生大量能量,但它们在游戏早期通常容易获得或成本低廉!\\n&7[Looking for early game power options? These are good ways to get you started with generating power.\\n\\nThese don't produce a ton of power, but they are typically easy or cheap to get in the early game!]&f"]
	quest.42D173B9FF8D16E4.quest_subtitle: "初始能源&7[Starter Power]&f"
	quest.42D173B9FF8D16E4.title: "&8&l&a游戏早期&f能源选项&7[lEarly Game Power Options]&f"
	quest.43D83CFA824B0A70.quest_desc: ["&9&d通用机械&f&r有一个终局能源选项,难以被超越.&d&a湮灭反应堆&f&r可以产生高达80 MRF/t的能量,如果你想学习如何建造它,一定要查看&a&d通用机械&f:&d反应堆&r任务章节!\\n&7[Mekanism has an end game power option that is tough to beat. The Fusion Reactor can produce up to 80MRF/t, and if you want to learn how to build it, make sure to check out the Mekanism: Reactors quest chapter!]&f"]
	quest.43D83CFA824B0A70.quest_subtitle: "聚变启动!&7[Fusion Activate!]&f"
	quest.43D83CFA824B0A70.title: "&9&d通用机械&f: &d&a湮灭反应堆&f&7[Mekanism: Fusion Reactor]&f"
	quest.477B411F84342EEA.quest_desc: ["&d通用机械&f是能量存储的最佳模组之一,尤其是在游戏早期.\\n\\n基础能量立方体易于配置,易于合成,并且存储大量能量.它也可以升级,并且可以在界面内为物品充电!\\n\\n要了解更多关于升级能量立方体以及该模组的信息,请前往&a&d通用机械&f&r任务章节!\\n&7[Mekanism is one of the best mods for energy storage, especially in the early game.\\n\\nThe Basic Energy Cube is easy to configure, easy to craft, and stores a lot of power. It can also be upgraded, and can charge items inside of the interface!\\n\\nTo learn more about upgrading the Energy Cube as well as the mod, head over to the Mekanism quest chapter!]&f"]
	quest.477B411F84342EEA.title: "&9&d通用机械&f:&a能量立方体&7[Mekanism: Energy Cubes]&f"
	quest.48DC9E8E9D21A2FA.quest_desc: ["&d通用机械&f提供了几种利用可再生资源发电的方式.\\n\\n&9&a太阳能发电模块&f&r利用太阳的能量来满足基本电力需求.它在夜晚不工作,并且必须能接触到天空.玻璃是可以的.\\n\\n&9&a风力发电机&f&r通过风提供能量.除非你想出了让你的角色手动旋转它的方法,否则它的旋转速度基于它所放置的Y坐标高度.它也需要直接接触天空,上方不能有任何方块.\\n&7[Mekanism provides several ways to make power using renewable resources.\\n\\nThe Solar Generators harness the power of the Sun to provide basic power needs. It does not work during the night, and must have access to the sky. Glass is okay.\\n\\nThe Wind Generator provides power via the wind. Unless you've figured out a way for your character to manually spin this, the speed it spins is based off of the Y lvl it is placed at. It also needs direct access to the sky without any blocks above it.]&f"]
	quest.48DC9E8E9D21A2FA.quest_subtitle: "&a太阳能&f……&7[The Power of the Sun...]&f"
	quest.48DC9E8E9D21A2FA.title: "&9&d通用机械&f: &a&a再生能源&f&7[Mekanism: Renewable Energy]&f"
	quest.4AB0DD227471FDBF.quest_desc: ["本章专门介绍所有与能量相关的内容!\\n\\n在这里,你将找到发电、存储和传输能量的基本方法.\\n&7[This chapter is dedicated to all things power related!\\n\\nHere you'll find the basic ways to generate, store, and transfer power.]&f"]
	quest.4AB0DD227471FDBF.quest_subtitle: "所有能量!&7[All The Power!]&f"
	quest.4AB0DD227471FDBF.title: "&c基础能源&7[Basic Power]&f"
	quest.4EEAB467C722ECE7.quest_desc: ["这些是简单的管道,可以用管道升级进行升级.\\n\\n要从一个方块”提取”能量,将管道放置在方块旁边,在连接的那一侧,按住Shift+右键点击管道扳手,将管道设置为提取模式.\\n\\n&e&lPipez&r模组还提供了运输物品、气体和液体的方式!或者你可以制作一个称为&a&a通用管道&f&r的多合一管道.\\n\\n其他扳手也可以与&e&lPipez&r一起使用!\\n&7[These are simple pipes that can be upgraded with Pipe Upgrades.\\n\\nTo 'extract' power from a block, place the pipe down next to the block, and on the side that is connected, shift+right-click with the pipe wrench to set the pipe to extract.\\n\\nThe lPipez mod also offers ways to transport items, gases, and liquids as well! Or you can make an All-In-One Pipe called the Universal Pipe.\\n\\nOther Wrenches work with lPipez as well!]&f"]
	quest.4EEAB467C722ECE7.title: "&9Pipez:&a&a能量管道&f&7[Pipez: Energy Pipes]&f"
	quest.56B6ABF3D6EA0D84.quest_desc: ["设置好我们的接入点后,我们现在可以从我们的网络中获取能量.&9&a通量接出点&f&r正是做这个的.它将你网络中的能量指向它所连接的任意方块,包括管道或线缆,或者直接连接到机器上!\\n\\n一旦你将接出点放置在你想要供电的机器或方块上,右键点击它,在”&a网络选择&f”标签页中选择你的网络.就像接入点一样,你可以调整接出点提取多少能量、优先级等.\\n&7[With our Plug set up, we can now tap into the power from our network. The Flux Point does exactly that. It points the power from your network to whatever block it is attached to, including Pipes or Cables, or just directly on machines!\\n\\nOnce you've placed your Point on the machine or block you want to power, right-click on it and select your network in the \"Network Selection\" tab. Just like the Plug, you can adjust how much power the Point pulls, priority level, etc.]&f"]
	quest.56B6ABF3D6EA0D84.title: "访问网络能量&7[Accessing Network Power]&f"
	quest.5C47935A3B2877FF.quest_desc: ["&d通用机械&f提供了一种外观不错的线缆来传输你的能量.\\n\\n如果你连接的机器已经可以拉取或推送能量,你就不需要配置线缆.否则,你需要一个&9配置器&r来配置线缆.按住Shift右键点击会将线缆更改为拉取或推送模式.\\n&7[Mekanism offers a nice looking Cable to transfer your power.\\n\\nIf the machine you are connecting to already pulls or pushes power, you will not need to configure the Cable. Otherwise, you'll need a Configurator to configure the Cable. Shift right-clicking will change the Cable to pull or push mode.]&f"]
	quest.5C47935A3B2877FF.quest_subtitle: "&d通用机械&f's &a能量传输&f Pipe&7[Mekanism's Energy Transfer Pipe]&f"
	quest.5C47935A3B2877FF.title: "&9&d通用机械&f:&a通用线缆&7[Mekanism: Universal Cables]&f"
	quest.5E41363F9AE243F3.quest_desc: ["你不能永远靠煤炭为你的基地供电!如果你有相当数量的可用资源,是时候升级你的能源设置了!\\n\\n这些选项通常需要一些设置,但产生的能量足以让你在游戏进程中走得很远.\\n&7[You can't power your base off of Coal forever! If you've got a decent amount of resources available, it's time to upgrade your power setup!\\n\\nThese options usually require a little setting up, but produce enough power to carry you far into your playthrough.]&f"]
	quest.5E41363F9AE243F3.title: "&b&l中期能源选项&7[lMid Game Power Options]&f"
	quest.5F078A574A783B02.quest_desc: ["启动你的通量网络所需的第一个物品是&9&a通量接入点&f&r.\\n\\n接入点用于从其连接的方块”抽取”能量.除了一个小缓冲区外,接入点本身不存储任何能量,所以不用担心它会吸走你所有的能量.\\n\\n建议将接入点放置在能量存储方块上,比如能量立方体.它可以连接到线缆、管道或任何发电机器的输出端.\\n\\n要学习如何设置你的第一个网络,请查看下一个任务!\\n&7[The first item you'll need to start your Flux Network is a Flux Plug.\\n\\nThe Plug is used to \"draw\" power from the block it is attached to. Aside from a small buffer, the Plug does not store any power itself, so don't worry about it zapping up all of your power.\\n\\nIt is suggested to place the Plug on a power storage block like an Energy Cube. It can connect to Cables, Pipes, or the output of any power producing machine.\\n\\nTo learn how to set up your first network, check the next quest!]&f"]
	quest.5F078A574A783B02.quest_subtitle: "插上它就行!&7[Just plug it in!]&f"
	quest.5F078A574A783B02.title: "启动你的网络&7[Starting Your Network]&f"
	quest.682034C680FDEDC2.quest_desc: [
		"&9&d通用机械&f&r的&a&a输导矩阵&f&r是一种强大的存储能量的方式.\\n\\n如果你在寻找&a&d通用机械&f&r提供的最佳能量存储,请查看&9&d通用机械&f:&r&d反应堆&r任务章节.\\n\\n&7[Mekanism's Induction Matrix is a powerful way to store your power.\\n\\nIf you're looking for the best power storage Mekanism has to offer, check out the Mekanism: Reactors quest chapter.\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_induction_matrix_small.png width:125 height:150 align:center fit:true}"
	]
	quest.682034C680FDEDC2.title: "More &a能量存储&f&7[More Power Storage]&f"
	quest.6D6E07564D8FDD8D.quest_desc: ["&a&d极限反应堆&f&r提供可完全自定义大小、效率等的多方块反应堆.\\n\\n要了解更多关于开始使用&d极限反应堆&f的信息,请查看该模组的任务章节!\\n&7[Extreme Reactors offers multi-block Reactors that are completely customizable in size, efficiency, and more.\\n\\nTo learn more about getting started with Extreme Reactors, check out the quest chapter for the mod!]&f"]
	quest.6D6E07564D8FDD8D.quest_subtitle: "可自定义的反应堆!&7[Customizable Reactors!]&f"
	quest.6D6E07564D8FDD8D.title: "&9&d极限反应堆&f:&a反应堆&7[Extreme Reactors: Reactors]&f"
	quest.72EA25D05C46D39A.quest_desc: ["&9&d动态联合/集成动力&f&r提供了一个简单的能量存储系统.&a电池&f可以在合成网格中组合以增加总存储量!\\n&7[Integrated Dynamics provides a simple power storage system. The Batteries can be combined in a crafting grid to increase the overall storage!]&f"]
	quest.72EA25D05C46D39A.quest_subtitle: "内含电池&7[Batteries Included]&f"
	quest.72EA25D05C46D39A.title: "&9&d动态联合/集成动力&f:&b能量电池&7[Integrated Dynamics: Energy Battery]&f"
	quest.76EA017B12E8F01B.quest_desc: ["本节向你展示存储能量的不同方式!\\n&7[This section shows you different ways to store your power!]&f"]
	quest.76EA017B12E8F01B.title: "&f&l存储能量&7[lStoring Power]&f"
	quest.79AD74A863EA43CB.quest_desc: ["&d通量网络&f确实提供了一种为你网络产生的能量存储的方式!\\n\\n这些总体上存储着大量的能量,并且可以升级以存储更多!\\n&7[Flux Networks does provide a way to store the power you generate for your network!\\n\\nThese hold massive amounts of power overall, and can be upgraded to store even more!]&f"]
	quest.79AD74A863EA43CB.quest_subtitle: "存储能量&7[Storing Power]&f"
	quest.79AD74A863EA43CB.title: "通量存储&7[Flux Storage]&f"
	quest.7A979BEB20C9591E.quest_desc: ["通量粉尘可以使用 &6&d资源蜜蜂&f&r 自动化生产!\\n\\n&a红石蜜蜂刷怪蛋&f 可以使用 &a黑曜石蜜蜂&f 转化为通量粉尘蜜蜂 &a刷怪蛋&f.\\n&7[Flux Dust can be automated using Productive Bees!\\n\\nRedstone Bee Spawn Eggs can be converted to Flux Dust Bee Spawn Eggs using an Obsidian Bee.]&f"]
	quest.7A979BEB20C9591E.title: "自动化通量粉尘&7[Automated Flux Dust]&f"
	quest.7FE969CB4B419FC6.quest_desc: ["稍微研究一下 &d通用机械&f,这台机器就能让你无线传输任何东西.\\n\\n你可以设置特定频道来传输单个物品、能量,甚至是 &d通用机械&f 中的气体.这相当酷.\\n&7[With a little work into Mekanism, this machine allows you to transfer anything wirelessly.\\n\\nYou can set specific channels to transfer individual items, energy, or even gases from Mekanism. It's pretty cool.]&f"]
	quest.7FE969CB4B419FC6.quest_subtitle: "不只传输能量&7[Doesn't just work for Power]&f"
	quest.7FE969CB4B419FC6.title: "&9&d通用机械&f: &6&a量子传送装置&f&7[Mekanism: Quantum Entangloporter]&f"
	task.098F1B932F851616.title: "管道升级&7[Pipe Upgrades]&f"
	task.2D0212699F99459F.title: "第一个网络&7[The First Network]&f"
	task.35C1DBD4544C9BB0.title: "感应单元&7[Induction Cells]&f"
	task.3D721B55E8D33FE8.title: "&d通量网络&f 用户界面&7[The Flux Networks UI]&f"
	task.44C02386C9B8E0D3.title: "感应供应器&7[Induction Providers]&f"
	task.59DE118DD6597A4E.title: "可再生 &d通用机械&f 能量发生器&7[Renewable Mekanism Energy Generators]&f"
	task.6C4B8A2662030CB0.title: "通用线缆&7[Universal Cables]&f"
	task.76378687551A79C3.title: "能量立方&7[Energy Cubes]&f"
	quest.01F59AF41A6DA0F7.quest_desc: ["&c致编辑模式用户:此任务已暂时隐藏,因为 &a飞龙奥法之镐&f 在撰写时没有合成配方.当 &a飞龙奥法之镐&f 可以通过 Forbidden Arcanus 或 KubeJS 制作时,请移除此注释并取消隐藏此任务.\\n&7[Note to those in Editing Mode: This quest was temporarily hidden as Draco Arcanus Pickaxe lacks a recipe at the time of writing. When Draco Arcanus Pickaxe becomes craftable, be it via Forbidden Arcanus or KubeJS, remove this note and unhide the quest.]&f"]
	quest.01F59AF41A6DA0F7.quest_subtitle: "等级:&54&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.03E05018D64DDEE1.quest_desc: ["&e等级 5&r 基本上只用于 &aATM矿石&f,其他用途不多.\\n&7[Tier 5 is basically just for ATM Ore, not much else.]&f"]
	quest.03E05018D64DDEE1.title: "&e采集等级 5&7[Harvest Tier 5]&f"
	quest.053E6882650CEFC6.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e5&7[Tier: 5]&f"
	quest.0583862ED0114442.quest_subtitle: "&f4 &c&a攻击伤害&f&7[4 Attack Damage]&f"
	quest.077A214422FEFF02.quest_subtitle: "&f6.5 &c&a攻击伤害&f&7[6.5 Attack Damage]&f"
	quest.09733948CBCB3FB9.quest_desc: ["&d等级 6&r 是最高等级,任何可破坏的方块都可以用它挖掘,包括振金和难得素.\\n&7[Tier 6 is the highest tier, anything that is breakable can be mined with it, including 振金 and 难得素.]&f"]
	quest.09733948CBCB3FB9.title: "&d采集等级 6&7[Harvest Tier 6]&f"
	quest.149BD1A9F82FA19A.quest_subtitle: "&f6 &c&a攻击伤害&f&7[6 Attack Damage]&f"
	quest.161878AB4236C58B.quest_subtitle: "&f6.5 &c&a攻击伤害&f&7[6.5 Attack Damage]&f"
	quest.16AAC61729C44881.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 工作人员&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 编写,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 AllTheMods 团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你能看到此信息,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.1756F81ACFC56C58.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e5&7[Tier: 5]&f"
	quest.175A03C28F72244D.quest_subtitle: "等级:&54&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.17FE0C7748DD65CA.quest_desc: ["&5等级 4&r 是钻石工具级别,用于获取黑曜石和下界合金.也包括一些模组矿石,如铀和铂.\\n&7[Tier 4 is Diamond tool level, used to get Obsidian and Netherite. Also some modded ores like Uranium and Platinum.]&f"]
	quest.17FE0C7748DD65CA.title: "&5采集等级 4&7[Harvest Tier 4]&f"
	quest.1D3F11194EA3BB73.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b3&7[Tier: 3]&f"
