	task.70972BAFF5896EA8.title: "&d神秘农业&f 镐&7[Mystical Agriculture Pickaxes]&f"
	task.7EA0E7DF4C5C4858.title: "应用能源2 镐&7[AE2 Pickaxes]&f"
	quest.102D82A38637FA84.quest_desc: ["&c&l&a心之容器&f&r 是一个以强力装备和提升最大生命值为核心的模组.主要资源是 &c 心&r,你可以通过击杀生物获得.不同的心来自不同的生物,低级心可以转化为更好的心.\\n&7[lBaubley Heart Canisters is a mod centered around strong gear and boosted max health. The main resource is  hearts, which you can get from killing mobs. Different hearts come from different mobs, and lower tier hearts can be turned into better ones.]&f"]
	quest.102D82A38637FA84.quest_subtitle: "窃取他们的心&7[Stealing their heart]&f"
	quest.102D82A38637FA84.title: "&c&l&a心之容器&f&7[lBaubley Heart Canisters]&f"
	quest.11AA616D7622370C.quest_desc: ["一个升级版本,可用于获得更多增益.\\n&7[An upgraded version that can be used for more buffs.]&f"]
	quest.15AEC638E00516AB.quest_subtitle: "一颗”冰冷”的心&7[A \"cold\" heart]&f"
	quest.29555A5CFB098858.quest_subtitle: "现在我们有所进展了&7[Now we're getting somewhere]&f"
	quest.297289FD3DA90DB4.quest_desc: ["几乎每一个敌对生物都会掉落一个 &c&a红心&f&r.这些用于游戏早期的生命值提升.\\n&7[Almost every single hostile mob drops a Red Heart. These are used for an early-game health boost.]&f"]
	quest.297289FD3DA90DB4.quest_subtitle: "别吃它!&7[Don't eat it!]&f"
	quest.2B0E41A8E9A34238.quest_subtitle: "花哨的创可贴&7[Fancy band-aid]&f"
	quest.30880CC59EEF97A8.quest_desc: ["你可以熔炼红心,并将它们与任何心”铸模”结合来制作一个黄心.\\n&7[You can melt down red hearts and combine them with any heart \"cast\" to make a yellow one.]&f"]
	quest.30880CC59EEF97A8.quest_subtitle: "就为了这一个？&7[All this for one?]&f"
	quest.30880CC59EEF97A8.title: "&a融化红心&f&7[Melted Red Hearts]&f"
	quest.31DE7556AC49EE48.quest_subtitle: "由龙(或非龙)制成&7[Made from dragons (or not)]&f"
	quest.49F4B5361AA39709.quest_desc: ["一个升级版本,可用于获得更多生命值.\\n&7[An upgraded version that can be used for more health.]&f"]
	quest.49F4B5361AA39709.quest_subtitle: "末影龙&7[Ender dragons]&f"
	quest.5902FDE5D2D74534.quest_subtitle: "强化的基础&7[The base for boosting]&f"
	quest.75ADA254B6B548D1.quest_desc: ["这足以在每次使用时完全恢复一整条生命值.相当不错!\\n&7[This is enough to full-heal an entire health bar per use. Pretty good!]&f"]
	quest.75ADA254B6B548D1.quest_subtitle: "20*50 = 1000 生命值&7[20*50 = 1000 health]&f"
	quest.0A497EC17534D248.quest_desc: ["&#53BAEDBBL 路由器&r 是一个完全无线的物流模组.你只需要 &#8B53ED输入器&r 和 &#EDB753输出器&r,它们就可以传输物品、流体、能量、化学品和源力.\\n&7[&#53BAEDBBL Routers is a logistics mod which is completely wireless. You just need the &#8B53EDImporters and &#EDB753Exporters and they can transfer items, fluids, power, chemicals and source.]&f"]
	quest.0A497EC17534D248.title: "&#45A5ED欢迎来到 BBL 路由器&7[&#45A5EDWelcome to BBL Routers]&f"
	quest.222446C143B43770.title: "传输源力&7[Transferring Source]&f"
	quest.33A1316FD66C6428.quest_subtitle: "输入器/输出器需要升级才能工作&7[Upgrades are required for the Importers/Exporters to work]&f"
	quest.3584DE12E1D7D14F.quest_desc: [
		"此模组中有两种类型的过滤器,你可以手持它们 &7右键点击&r 来设置:\\n&7[There are 2 types of filters in this mod, you can right-click with them in hand to set them:]&f"
		""
		"1. &#EDDE53&a模组过滤器&f&r:你必须输入模组的完整名称(不含空格)来设置过滤器.\\n&7[1. &#EDDE53Mod Filter: You have to write the full name of the mod without spaces to set the filter.]&f"
		""
		"2. &#EDDE53&a标签过滤器&f&r:你必须输入标签(不带 # 号)来设置过滤器.\\n&7[2. &#EDDE53Tag Filter: You have to write the tag without the # to set the filter.]&f"
	]
	quest.3584DE12E1D7D14F.title: "过滤器升级&7[Filter Upgrades]&f"
	quest.3E14842D5F454F98.title: "提高操作速度&7[Increasing Operation Speed]&f"
	quest.401A518B2D1BDB9A.quest_subtitle: "放置在接收容器上&7[Place on the receiving inventory]&f"
	quest.5312BD7BDC054E48.title: "传输物品&7[Transferring Items]&f"
	quest.548676DCD1E09A7F.quest_subtitle: "放置在发送容器上&7[Place on the sender inventory]&f"
	quest.6420E8B38993D8E3.title: "能量传输&7[Power Transmission]&f"
	quest.671141CF874D89A4.title: "传输流体&7[Transferring Fluids]&f"
	quest.68ABBA8CB99AF6A1.quest_desc: [
		"将鼠标悬停在物品上并按住 &#EDD353Shift&r 键,将获得相关信息.\\n&7[Holding &#EDD353Shift over an item will give you information regarding them.]&f"
		""
		"要使用 &#537CED连接器&r,首先 &7右键点击&r &#EDB553输入器&r,然后 &7右键点击&r &#5360ED输出器&r 来连接它们.\\n&7[To use the &#537CEDConnector, first right-click on the &#EDB553Importer and then right-click on &#5360EDExporter to link them.]&f"
	]
	quest.6B11A21220723520.title: "传输化学品&7[Transferring Chemicals]&f"
	quest.7742D896461A4632.quest_subtitle: "只需将其放入输出器&7[Just put it in the Exporter]&f"
	task.368EEAEC5B950F4D.title: "使用连接器&7[Using the Connector]&f"
	task.7ECFB3665B40F251.title: "升级&7[Upgrades]&f"
	quest.08B60D8A25008CCC.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 工作人员&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 编写,用于 AllTheMods 整合包. \\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 AllTheMods 团队发布的公开整合包. \\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你能看到此信息,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.09C82CDDA800D8C9.quest_desc: ["&a凋灵&f是《我的世界》中的第二个Boss,这个Boss的出现更具选择性.\\n\\n你需要建造凋灵来生成它.用4个&a灵魂沙&f摆成T形,并在顶部放置3个&a凋灵骷髅头颅&f即可生成它!\\n\\n它拥有300点生命值,会四处飞行并向玩家或生物发射&a凋灵之首&f.\\n\\n当生命值降至一半时,它会获得一个针对弹射物的护盾,需要用剑或斧头才能杀死它.\\n\\n一旦你杀死它,它会掉落:&a下界之星&f,有几率掉落&a凋灵灵魂碎片&f,以及大量Corail物品.\\n&7[The Wither is the second Minecraft Boss, this one being more elective. \\n\\nYou'll have to build the Wither to spawn him in. Using 4 Soul Sand in a T shape and placing 3 Wither Skeleton Skulls on top will spawn him in! \\n\\nHe has 300 Hearts and will fly around shooting Wither Skulls at Players or Mobs. \\n\\nWhen taken to half Health he will gain a shield against Projectiles and will need to be killed with a Sword or Axe. \\n\\nOnce you kill him he'll drop: Nether Star, chance at a Withering Soul, and a ton of Corail Items.]&f"]
	quest.09C82CDDA800D8C9.title: "击杀 &a凋灵&f&7[Kill The Wither]&f"
	quest.0E20A9B79D1C6637.quest_desc: ["&a监守者&f是1.20版本中加入的Boss.\\n\\n当3个自然生成的&a幽匿尖啸体&f连续被触发,或者在第一个监守者生成后有任何尖啸体被触发时,它就会生成.\\n\\n它是《我的世界》中加入的最强大的生物,拥有500点生命值,攻击伤害超过20点.\\n\\n它的攻击包括近战击打和对远处目标的声纳冲击.\\n\\n它唯一的弱点是失明,但就像夜魔侠一样,这反而让它的其他感官变得更加强大!如果你靠近,它能闻到你的气味,并且要小心不要发出噪音!\\n\\n如果你设法杀死了它,它会掉落:&a幽匿催发体&f、监守者甲壳和深暗之心.\\n&7[The Warden is a boss added in 1.20. \\n\\nHe spawns by having 3 naturally spawning Sculk Shriekers going off in a row, or any Shriekers going off after a first Warden has spawned. \\n\\nHe is the most powerful Mob added by Minecraft, with 500 Hearts and over 20 Hearts damage with his attacks. \\n\\nHis attacks include hitting you and Sonar Blasts for those farther. \\n\\nHis only weakness is being blind, but like daredevil it just made his other senses much stronger! If you are close he can smell you and careful with making noise! \\n\\nIf you somehow kill him he will drop: Sculk Catalysts, Warden Carapace, and Heart of the Deep.]&f"]
	quest.0E20A9B79D1C6637.title: "杀死&a监守者&f&7[Kill The Warden]&f"
	quest.0F55D0B4D5094EDB.quest_desc: ["在为ATM7制作大量任务线时,村民商人觉得在任务界面里不断推搡我很有趣.\\n\\n”干掉他们.全部干掉.”\\n\\n- AlfredGG \\n\\n”我附议!” \\n\\n- Toshiba\\n&7[While making a lot of the questlines for ATM7, the Trader Villager thought it'd be funny to constantly push me around in the quest screen.\\n\\n\"Take them out. All of them.\"\\n\\n- AlfredGG \\n\\n\"I second this!\" \\n\\n- Toshiba]&f"]
	quest.0F55D0B4D5094EDB.quest_subtitle: "“私人恩怨“ - AlfredGG&7[\"This is Personal\" - AlfredGG]&f"
	quest.0F55D0B4D5094EDB.title: "杀死 &a流浪商人&f 及其烦人的羊驼&7[Kill The Trader Villager and His Annoying Llamas]&f"
	quest.17F3AC15ADCFB175.title: "&l&9末地悬赏:&r&e 末影人&7[lThe End Bounty: Endermen]&f"
	quest.1F18B64C84C8809D.title: "&l&9主世界悬赏:&r&e 蜘蛛&7[lOverworld Bounty: Spiders]&f"
	quest.2B05A29C62676EB2.title: "&l&9主世界悬赏:&r&e 僵尸&7[lOverworld Bounty: Zombies]&f"
	quest.2BD077EFE77B8EBB.quest_desc: ["僵尸有不同的变种,它们生成于其他生物群系.\\n&7[Zombies have different variants that spawn in other Biomes. ]&f"]
	quest.2BD077EFE77B8EBB.title: "僵尸变种&7[Zombie Variants]&f"
	quest.3371F9248D403664.title: "&l&c&a下界&f 悬赏:&r&e &a凋灵骷髅&f&7[lThe Nether Bounty: Wither Skeletons]&f"
	quest.3813F5C1760C3A79.quest_desc: ["&a猪灵蛮兵&f 出现在这里可能会引起争议,但我认为它们是迷你Boss.\\n\\n它们与普通猪灵一同生成于堡垒遗迹中,但它们是敌对而非中立的.我个人很讨厌这点,尤其是因为如果你攻击它们,所有猪灵都会对你转为敌对.\\n\\n它们有 50 颗心,并用一把 &a金斧&f 攻击你.通常 &a金斧&f 几乎造不成什么伤害,但当它们使用时,不知为何却威力无穷!\\n\\n它们不掉落任何物品,更像是堡垒遗迹中的障碍物!\\n&7[Piglin Brutes being here might cause controversy but I consider them Minibosses. \\n\\nThey spawn in Bastions with regular Piglins but these are Hostile not Neutral. Personally I hate that, especially since if you hit them all Piglins will turn Hostile on you. \\n\\nThey have 50 Hearts and a Golden Axe to hit you. Usually Golden Axes barely do any damage, but when they use it, it is god somehow! \\n\\nThey drop nothing and act more like an obstacle for Bastions!]&f"]
	quest.3813F5C1760C3A79.title: "杀死一个 &a猪灵蛮兵&f&7[Kill A Piglin Brute]&f"
	quest.41C0948CD9D50322.quest_desc: ["在这里,你将找到通过击杀敌人可以获得的所有奖励.\\n&7[Here you'll find all of the rewards you can get by slaying enemies.]&f"]
	quest.41C0948CD9D50322.quest_subtitle: "杀光所有东西&7[Killing All The Things]&f"
	quest.41C0948CD9D50322.title: "&a悬赏榜&f&7[Bounty Board]&f"
	quest.42822B1E8A53D051.title: "&l&9主世界悬赏:&r&e 骷髅&7[lOverworld Bounty: Skeletons]&f"
	quest.56DA46DC82F6665D.quest_desc: ["&a荒野奇美拉&f 是由 &d新生魔艺&f 添加的一个Boss,是推进该模组进程所必需的.\\n\\n需要通过仪式召唤,然后与之战斗!\\n&7[The Wilden Chimera is a Boss added by Ars Nouveau and is needed for progressing through it. \\n\\nHe needs to be summoned through a ritual then fought!]&f"]
	quest.56DA46DC82F6665D.title: "杀死 &a荒野奇美拉&f&7[Kill The Wilden Chimera]&f"
	quest.5AC497F76A086A5C.title: "&l&9主世界悬赏:&r&e 女巫&7[lOverworld Bounty: Witches]&f"
	quest.6141DE779232C8AA.title: "&l&c&a下界&f 悬赏:&r&e 烈焰人&7[lThe Nether Bounty: Blazes]&f"
	quest.6827836C8E675A94.quest_desc: ["骷髅有不同的变种,就像僵尸一样!\\n&7[Skeletons have different variants, like Zombies do!]&f"]
	quest.6827836C8E675A94.title: "骷髅变种&7[Skeleton Variants]&f"
	quest.728BE1816DA23DC0.quest_desc: ["&a末影龙&f 是守卫末地的Boss.\\n\\n当你进入一个 &a末地传送门&f 时,你会到达她生成的那个末地岛屿.\\n\\n她有 200 颗心,可以用火球攻击或冲撞你.\\n\\n你必须破坏黑曜石柱上的 &a末影水晶&f,因为它们会治疗她,这样才能杀死她!\\n\\n一旦你杀死了她,她会掉落:奥术精华、史诗级着色袋、龙皮、来自两个不同模组的 &a龙鳞&f,以及一大堆经验!\\n\\n然后传送门会打开,你可以返回主世界,或者你可以找到一个 &a末地折跃门&f 去探索外岛.你还会在传送门上找到一个 &a龙蛋&f.\\n&7[The Ender Dragon is the Boss that guards The End. \\n\\nWhen you enter an End Portal you'll arrive at the End Island where she spawns. \\n\\nShe has 200 Hearts and can attack with Fireballs or ramming into you. \\n\\nYou'll have to break the End Crystals on the pillars as they heal her, in order to kill her! \\n\\nOnce you do kill her, she'll drop: Arcane Essence, Epic Shaderbags, Dragonskin, Dragon Scales from two different mods, and a bunch of experience! \\n\\nThen the Portal will open up so you can return to the Overworld, or you can find an End Gateway to explore the outer islands. You'll also find a Dragon Egg on the Portal.]&f"]
	quest.728BE1816DA23DC0.title: "杀死 &a末影龙&f&7[Kill The Ender Dragon]&f"
	quest.77FC692AC94D2EEF.title: "&l&9主世界悬赏:&r&e 苦力怕&7[lOverworld Bounty: Creepers]&f"
	task.00CBF98DE4E9CC90.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.171FD27057746E80.title: "杀死 1 个凋灵&7[Kill 1 Wither]&f"
	task.1809F1F9A3043683.title: "杀死 1 个 &a末影龙&f&7[Kill 1 Ender Dragon]&f"
	task.1D136D138EF82DA9.title: "杀死 2 只行商羊驼&7[Kill 2 Trader Llamas]&f"
	task.452B65E139D9E12D.title: "Kill 1 &a荒野奇美拉&f&7[Kill 1 Wilden Chimera]&f"
	task.596ABB45C0612AAF.title: "杀死 1 个流浪商人&7[Kill 1 Wandering Trader]&f"
	task.65E53C9C5AE98B69.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.69678CAC075C8EA5.title: "杀死 1 个监守者&7[Kill 1 Warden]&f"
	quest.0052E5592A6BBEC1.quest_desc: [
		"这是 &2&lMinecraft&r,我不能教你如何建造……\\n&7[This is lMinecraft, I can't tell you how to build...]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"但我可以给你一些建议!\\n&7[But I can give you tips for it!]&f"
	]
	quest.0052E5592A6BBEC1.title: "&l建造小贴士!&r&7[lBuilding Tips!]&f"
	quest.01516BC726013B7C.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 工作人员&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 创作,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.034DB3C64F24C7B7.quest_desc: ["&6&lAllTheOres&r 是一个内部制作的模组,旨在帮助统一矿石.\\n\\n随之而来的是一大堆非常有用的装饰性方块!\\n\\n&d萤石&r 和 &9蓝宝石&r 看起来都非常酷!\\n&7[lAllTheOres is a built in-house mod made to help unify ores.\\n\\nWith that comes a ton of very useful decorative blocks!\\n\\nFluorite and Sapphire both look very cool!]&f"]
	quest.034DB3C64F24C7B7.title: "&l&6AllTheOres&r 方块&7[lAllTheOres Blocks]&f"
	quest.04F5846E2468E807.quest_desc: ["&b&lMacaw's Doors&r 添加了各种不同的门及其变种.\\n你想要白桦木的设计但用的是 &a白桦木&f？你可以拥有它!\\n\\n天哪,它甚至还有医院门!\\n&7[lMacaw's Doors adds all sorts of different Doors and variants of Doors. \\nYou want the Birch design but with Spruce Wood? You can have it! \\n\\nHeck it even has Hospital Doors!]&f"]
	quest.04F5846E2468E807.title: "&b&lMacaw的门&7[lMacaw's Doors]&f"
	quest.0539AF15A10B2859.quest_desc: ["&l&d更多空间/压缩空间&f&r 允许你进入一个压缩维度.放置一个 &l&a压缩空间机械&f&r 后,你可以使用 &a个人缩放设备&f 进入它.\\n\\n&l&a压缩空间机械&f&r 的大小取决于配方,范围从 5x5x5 到 45x45x45!\\n\\n你无法破坏 &l&a压缩空间机械&f&r 的墙壁,可以通过 &a右击&f &a个人缩放设备&f 退出.\\n&7[lCompact Machines allow you to enter a compacted dimension. After placing a lCompact Machine, you can enter it using the Personal Shrinking Device.\\n\\nThe size of the lCompact Machine is dependent on the recipe, ranging from 5x5x5 to 45x45x45!\\n\\nYou can't break the lCompact Machine's walls, and you can exit by Right Clicking the Personal Shrinking Device.]&f"]
	quest.0539AF15A10B2859.title: "&l&d更多空间/压缩空间&f&7[lCompact Machines]&f"
	quest.0596F6C70758EEC0.quest_desc: ["虽然是最昂贵的,但它们也是最漂亮的!\\n\\n而这对于建筑来说才是最重要的!\\n&7[While being the most expensive, they also are the prettiest! \\n\\nAnd that is what matters for Builds!]&f"]
	quest.06FFBB12CFA87815.quest_desc: ["来自 &2原版 &lMinecraft&r 的原木,可以在不同的 &2原版&r 生物群系中找到!\\n\\n我不需要再解释更多了!\\n&7[The Logs from Vanilla lMinecraft, found in the different Vanilla Biomes! \\n\\nI shouldn't have to explain anymore than that!]&f"]
	quest.06FFBB12CFA87815.title: "&2原版&r 原木&7[Vanilla Logs]&f"
	quest.08C66BCA3AAE765B.quest_desc: ["这个模组添加的是非 &2&lMinecraft&r 方块,所以我宁愿不讨论它.\\n&7[This one adds Non-lMinecraft Blocks so I'd rather not discuss it.]&f"]
	quest.08C66BCA3AAE765B.title: "&b&lMacaw的屋顶&7[lMacaw's Roofs]&f"
	quest.09955CF85F579E0F.quest_desc: ["你最终会得到这个,它简直是 &2&lMinecraft&r 中最丰富的方块.\\n&7[You'll get this eventually, it's quite literally the most abundant Block in lMinecraft.]&f"]
	quest.09955CF85F579E0F.title: "石质方块&7[Stone Blocks]&f"
	quest.09F49ED309152E24.quest_desc: ["&l&cChisel Reborn&r 是另一个基于 &l凿子&r 的模组.\\n\\n该模组的本质是使用凿子工具来改变某些方块的设计.\\n\\n你可以用凿子 &a右击&f 来打开其 GUI,在那里你可以放入最多一组方块,然后选择你想要的设计,再取出来.或者你可以把它留在凿子里,不过我不明白你为什么要这么做.\\n\\n你也可以用凿子 &a左击&f 一个方块来改变其设计,而无需打开凿子 GUI!\\n\\n别担心,这个没有耐久度.\\n&7[lChisel Reborn is another Mod based off of lChiseled. \\n\\nThe essence of the Mod is using the Chisel Tool to change the designs of some Blocks. \\n\\nYou can Right Click with the Chisel to open its GUI, there you can put up to a stack of Blocks into it, then choose a design you want, and take it out. Or you can keep it in the Chisel, I don't see why you would want to though. \\n\\nYou can also Left Click a Block with the Chisel to change its design without opening the Chisel GUI! \\n\\nDon't worry this one doesn't have Durability.]&f"]
	quest.09F49ED309152E24.title: "&l&c凿子工艺:重生&r&7[lChisel Reborn]&f"
	quest.0A21773B773F34F8.quest_desc: ["颜色是让建筑更具活力的最重要部分之一!\\n\\n它赋予建筑生命、个性和色彩!\\n\\n从染料开始吧!\\n&7[Color is one of the most important parts of making a Build more lively! \\n\\nIt gives it life, personality, and color! \\n\\nStart with the Dyes!]&f"]
	quest.0A21773B773F34F8.title: "彩色方块&7[Colored Blocks]&f"
	quest.0EB6ED88895366D0.quest_desc: ["还记得当初只有石头和圆石的时候吗？\\n&7[Remember when it was just Stone and Cobblestone?]&f"]
	quest.0EB6ED88895366D0.title: "&2原版&r 石质方块&7[Vanilla Stones]&f"
	quest.0FE30548F25FEDB1.quest_desc: ["如果你像我一样不喜欢住在盒子里(这让我太多地想起了学校),那么你会喜欢在建筑中使用玻璃来看到外面.\\n\\n当然,普通的原版玻璃不错,但我们可以做得更好!\\n\\n我们甚至可以从它身上获得一些用处!\\n&7[If you're like me and don't like living in a Box (it reminds me too much of School), then you'll like to have Glass in your Builds to see outside. \\n\\nWhile the normal Vanilla ones are nice of course we can do much better! \\n\\nWe can even get some use out of it!]&f"]
	quest.106884349C9FF3BA.quest_desc: ["伙计,有些 &a光源&f 真是丑得要命!\\n\\n让我们改变这一点!\\n&7[Man some Light Sources are just so butt ugly! \\n\\nLets change that!]&f"]
	quest.106884349C9FF3BA.title: "&l&bChipped&r 光源&7[lChipped Lights]&f"
	quest.11C43962B06D5092.quest_desc: ["这有必要吗？\\n&7[Is this necessary?]&f"]
	quest.11C43962B06D5092.title: "现在你只是在炫耀&7[Now you're just showing off]&f"
	quest.156605859D553276.quest_desc: ["窗户、窗格、百叶窗、窗帘、百叶帘,甚至护墙!\\n\\n我甚至不知道那是什么!\\n&7[Windows, Windows Panes, Winder Shutters, Curtains, Blinds, to even Parapets! \\n\\nI don't even know what that is!]&f"]
	quest.156605859D553276.title: "&l&bMacaw的窗户&r&7[lMacaw's Windows]&f"
	quest.1591013DDD4766E1.quest_desc: ["&l&c&d懒人厨房&f&r 的全部意义在于让厨房成为你的家.\\n\\n我推荐使用它提供的所有物品,因为每件物品都有用且看起来很棒!\\n&7[lCooking for Blockheads is all about making the Kitchen your home. \\n\\nI recommend using everything it gives as every Item has a use and looks amazing!]&f"]
	quest.1591013DDD4766E1.title: "&l&c&d懒人厨房&f&r&7[lCooking for Blockheads]&f"
	quest.1972B36F72808D55.quest_desc: ["不过这些石头中只有一部分是经过”雕琢”的.\\n&7[Only some of theses stones are chipped though.]&f"]
	quest.1972B36F72808D55.title: "&l&bChipped&r 石质方块&7[lChipped Stones]&f"
	quest.1FD60B7448CED1EB.quest_desc: ["这个 &b&lMacaw&r 模组添加了新型的栅栏、门和墙.\\n\\n是的,带刺铁丝网会伤害你.\\n\\n不,你通常无法跳过它们中的任何一个.\\n&7[This lMacaw Mod adds new types of Fences, Gates, and Walls. \\n\\nYes, the barbed wire will hurt you. \\n\\nNo, you can't jump over any of them normally.]&f"]
	quest.1FD60B7448CED1EB.title: "&b&lMacaw的栅栏和墙&7[lMacaw's Fences and Walls]&f"
	quest.2094D1CE4BA66091.quest_desc: ["光照是任何基地非常重要的一部分.\\n\\n它能防止怪物生成,帮助看清东西,甚至能为你的建筑增添更多色彩和生机!\\n\\n或者你也可以只用 &a夜视&f 效果,但那有什么乐趣呢!\\n&7[Light is a very important part of any Base. \\n\\nIt keeps Monsters from Spawning, helps to see, and even adds more Color and life to your Builds! \\n\\nOr you can just use Night Vision but where's the fun in that!]&f"]
	quest.22D2CFDDB06C720C.quest_desc: ["工具在 &2&lMinecraft&r 中非常重要,但物品栏空间也同样重要.所以,为什么不制作一把万用工具来腾出一些空间呢!\\n万用工具是镐(P)、斧(axe)和锹(els)的组合.\\n\\n它们可以剥树皮、铺路,并且可以挖掘同等级镐/斧/锹能挖掘的任何方块!\\n&7[Tools are very important in lMinecraft but so is inventory space. So why not clear some space up by making a Paxel! \\nPaxels are a combination of Pickaxes (P), Axes (axe), and Shovels (els). \\n\\nThey can strip wood, make paths, and mine any blocks that same pickaxe/axe/shovel tier can!]&f"]
	quest.22D2CFDDB06C720C.title: "万用工具&7[Paxel]&f"
	quest.23631A4A743D4F0C.quest_desc: ["这个就别抱怨了.\\n\\n有几十种方法可以获得铁,即使是正常推进游戏进程也需要它.\\n\\n你会得到铁,你会把它做成方块,而且你会让它变得漂亮!\\n&7[Don't even complain about this one. \\n\\nThere are dozens of ways of getting Iron and it's needed for even just normal progression. \\n\\nYou will get Iron, you will make it into a Block, and you will make it pretty!]&f"]
	quest.23631A4A743D4F0C.title: "&l&bChipped&r 金属方块&7[lChipped Metals]&f"
	quest.26FADB78B04F592B.quest_desc: ["&l&a&d建筑小帮手&f 2&r 是一个添加了几个非常有用的物品的模组.\\n\\n当然,所有这些都是为了建造!\\n\\n每个都需要 &c能量&r 才能工作,并且有一个菜单,默认按 &lG&r 键打开.\\n&7[lBuilding Gadgets 2 is a Mod that adds a few very helpful Items. \\n\\nAll for of course, building! \\n\\nEach requires Energy to work and has a Menu which is pulled up by default lG.]&f"]
	quest.26FADB78B04F592B.title: "&l&a&d建筑小帮手&f&r&7[lBuilding Gadgets]&f"
	quest.28FDB2D13D0DDE8E.quest_desc: ["&b&lChipped&r 类似于凿子模组,因为它改变了方块的设计,但 &b&lChipped&r 有自己独特的方式!\\n\\n&b&lChipped&r 使用的是你需要前往的工作站来改变方块.\\n\\n有 7 个不同的工作站,每个改变不同的方块:木工台改变木材,玻璃吹制台改变玻璃.\\n\\n其中 6 个工作站可以变成手持物品以便于使用.\\n\\n甚至还有它们的背包升级!\\n&7[lChipped is similar to Chisels Mods as it changes the designs of Blocks, but lChipped has their own way of doing so! \\n\\nlChipped instead uses Stations you'll need to go to, to change Blocks. \\n\\nThere's 7 different Stations each change different Blocks: Carpenters Table changes Wood, Glassblower changes Glass. \\n\\nAnd 6 of those Stations can be changed into a handheld Item for easier access. \\n\\nThere's even Backpack Upgrades for them!]&f"]
	quest.28FDB2D13D0DDE8E.title: "&l&b巧工妙艺&r&7[lChipped]&f"
	quest.2B4801CD3E90BD40.quest_desc: ["&l&3Handcrafted&r 是为了所有装饰方面的东西.\\n\\n有床(看起来好到可以睡进去,我可是个挑剔的睡眠者!)和床头柜用于卧室.\\n\\n有椅子和桌子用于 &a客厅&f.\\n\\n有烤箱、盘子和碗用于厨房.\\n\\n天哪,甚至还有雕像,就为了炫耀!\\n&7[lHandcrafted is for everything Decoration wise. \\n\\nThere's Beds (that look good enough to sleep in, and I'm a picky sleeper!) and Nightstands for the Bedrooms. \\n\\nThere's Chairs and Tables for Living Room. \\n\\nThere's an Oven, Plates, and Bowls for the Kitchen. \\n\\nHeck there's even Statues just for showing off!]&f"]
	quest.2B4801CD3E90BD40.title: "&l&3匠心手作&r&7[lHandcrafted]&f"
	quest.2B864D741F7C7549.quest_desc: ["&l&d林业&f&r 全是关于树木和培育树木以制造更多树木.\\n\\n所以你可以放心地猜测它为 &2&lMinecraft&r 带来了更多木材类型!\\n\\n天哪,甚至还有一些特殊木材!\\n&7[lProductive Trees is all about Trees and Breeding Trees to make more Trees. \\n\\nSo you are safe to guess it brings more Wood types to lMinecraft! \\n\\nHeck even some specialty Wood!]&f"]
	quest.2B864D741F7C7549.title: "&l&d林业&f&7[lProductive Trees]&f"
	quest.2BA0E5D48E234FE9.quest_desc: ["&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r 的魔法领域为我们带来了魔光!纯粹的魔法 &a光源&f!\\n\\n它们可以通过法术正常放置,或者你可以制作一个 &a魔光灯笼&f 并放置它.\\n&7[The magical realm of lArs Nouveau brings us Magelights! Light Sources of pure magic! \\n\\nThey can either be placed normally using Spells or you can craft a Magelight Lantern and place that instead.]&f"]
	quest.2BA0E5D48E234FE9.title: "&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r 光源&7[lArs Nouveau Lights]&f"
	quest.30B3BC91460C9B19.quest_desc: ["&bMacaw Sketch&r 是一位非常受欢迎的模组开发者.他以装饰模组而闻名.\\n从窗户,到小径,再到抽屉.他几乎什么都做.\\n\\n你能把它们都制作出来吗？\\n&7[Macaw Sketch is a very popular Mod Developer. He is known for Decor Mods. \\nFrom Windows, to Pathways, to Drawers. He makes just about everything. \\n\\nCan you craft it all?]&f"]
	quest.30B3BC91460C9B19.title: "&bMacaw的模组&7[Macaw's Mods]&f"
	quest.318A2CC03D1D0B04.quest_desc: ["是否怀念 &l&a建造用星杖&f&r？\\n\\n我很怀念,&9Mrbysco&r 也是!所以他制作了 &l&6建造手杖&r!\\n\\n&6建造手杖&r 有几个不同的等级.越昂贵的手杖,耐久度越高,能放置的方块也越多.\\n\\n它们最初只是放置方块来填充空间,但可以通过打开其 GUI 来更改选项.你需要自己设置一个按键绑定来打开它.\\n\\n打开后,你可以更改关于它们的一切:在哪里放置方块、以何种模式放置,甚至放置什么方块!\\n\\n它们还有自己可以合成的升级.要使用升级,请在 &a锻造台&f 中将升级与你的 &6建造手杖&r 结合.\\n&7[Ever miss lConstruction Wands? \\n\\nWell I did, and so did Mrbysco! So he made lConstruction Sticks! \\n\\nThere's a few different Tier of Construction Stick. The more expensive they are, the more Durability they have and the more Blocks they can place. \\n\\nThey will start by just placing Blocks to fill a space, but their options can be changed by opening their GUI. You'll need to set a Keybind yourself to do it. \\n\\nOnce you open it, you can change everything about them. Where they place Blocks, in what pattern, and even what Blocks to place down! \\n\\nThey also have their own Upgrades you can Craft. To use them, combine the Upgrade with your Construction Stick in a Smithing Table. ]&f"]
	quest.318A2CC03D1D0B04.title: "&l&6建造手杖&7[lConstruction Sticks]&f"
	quest.3497C2E05DF5A87C.quest_desc: ["&c红石&r、&9青金石&r、石英、&5紫水晶&r、&a绿宝石&r 和 &b钻石&r 都是珍贵的宝石.\\n\\n所以我们当然要把它们变成方块,确切地说是非常漂亮的珍贵方块!\\n&7[Redstone, Lapis, Quartz, Amethyst, Emerald, and Diamonds are all precious Gems. \\n\\nSo of course we are turning them into Blocks, very pretty precious Blocks to be exact!]&f"]
	quest.3497C2E05DF5A87C.title: "&l&bChipped&r 宝石方块&7[lChipped Gem Blocks]&f"
	quest.35C46E6E27C9CB1A.quest_desc: ["10 种 &2原版&r 原木很棒,但它们的样式有限!\\n\\n所以 &l&bChipped&r 当然要加入,为这些原木添加了数十种新设计!\\n&7[The 10 Vanilla Logs are wonderful, but they only have so many designs! \\n\\nSo of course lChipped, chipped in by adding dozens of new designs for those Logs!]&f"]
	quest.35C46E6E27C9CB1A.title: "&l&bChipped&r 原木&7[lChipped Logs]&f"
	quest.3889D0255074CE85.quest_desc: ["&bMacaw&r 觉得家具还不够,他的 Macaw 之家需要比 &b&lMacaw 窗户&r 的自然光更多的东西.\\n\\n所以现在我们有了 &b&lMacaw 的灯饰&r,它添加了各种 &a光源&f.\\n\\n从灯到灯笼再到枝形吊灯!\\n&7[Macaw decided the furniture wasn't enough, he needed his Macaw home to have more than just natural lighting from his lMacaw Windows. \\n\\nSo now we have lMacaw's Lights and Lamps which adds all sorts of Light Sources. \\n\\nFrom Lamps to Lanterns to Chanderliers!]&f"]
	quest.3889D0255074CE85.title: "&l&bMacaw 的灯饰&r&7[lMacaw's Lights and Lamps]&f"
	quest.392F34FD4FCC794A.quest_desc: ["虽然它们可能价格不菲,但也非常时尚!\\n&7[While they can be expensive they're also plenty stylish!]&f"]
	quest.392F34FD4FCC794A.title: "&2&l&d神秘农业&f&r 方块&7[lMystical Agriculture Blocks]&f"
	quest.3BA4504DEFB87264.quest_desc: ["工作原理与 &l&a简易光源&f&r 类似,反转版本在没有红石信号时会亮起,而普通版本只在有红石信号时工作.\\n\\n不过,这些灯需要附着在墙上才能放置.\\n&7[Works similar to the lSimply Lights, Inverted will Light when no Redstone is applied to it while normal will only work with Redstone. \\n\\nThese need to be attached to a Wall to be placed though.]&f"]
	quest.3BA4504DEFB87264.title: "&a壁灯&f&7[Wall Lamps]&f"
	quest.3D1D5CB45D81A6E4.quest_desc: ["与 &b&lMacaw's Doors&r 类似,这个模组添加了不同类型和版本的活板门.\\n\\n你想要一个带有云杉图案的 &a丛林木活板门&f 吗？现在你可以做到了!\\n&7[Similar to lMacaw's Doors this one adds different types and versions of Trapdoors. \\n\\nYou want a Jungle Trapdoor with the Spruce Pattern? Well now you can! ]&f"]
	quest.3D1D5CB45D81A6E4.title: "&b&lMacaw 的活板门&7[lMacaw's Trapdoors]&f"
	quest.3E4B27759C973006.quest_desc: ["&l&6Framed Blocks&r 是最重要的建筑模组.事实上,如果你给我一个整合包,里面没有 &l&6Framed Blocks&r,我是不会玩的.它就是如此重要!\\n\\n&l&6Framed Blocks&r 为我们提供了框架方块,可以用任何非方块实体(方块实体是指像工作台、熔炉或 &a富集仓&f 这样的方块)来填充.\\n\\n这些框架几乎可以是任何形状或任何东西!从垂直台阶,到斜坡,甚至是四分之一方块!\\n\\n你想要 &5下界合金&r 楼梯？那就用框架方块!你想要一个干草捆工作台？你可以做到!你想要在建筑中获得完美的角度？那就开始制作 &l&6Framed Blocks&r 吧!\\n&7[lFramed Blocks is the single most important Building Mod. Infact if you give me a Modpack and lFramed Blocks is not in it, I won't play. It is that important! \\n\\nlFramed Blocks gives us mock Blocks that can be filled in with any Block that isn't a Block Entity (Block Entities are Blocks like Crafting Table, Furnace, or Enrichment Chamber). \\n\\nThese Frames can be just about any shape or anything! From vertical Slabs, to slopes, even quarter blocks! \\n\\nYou want Netherite Stairs? Then use Framed Blocks! You want a Haybale Crafting Table? You can get it! You want perfect angles in your build? Then start making lFramed Blocks!]&f"]
	quest.3E4B27759C973006.title: "&l&6框架方块&r&7[lFramed Blocks]&f"
	quest.3ED8365BAD406CC5.quest_desc: ["这些是我发现的非常适合装饰你的房子或基地的模组!\\n\\n尽管去探索比这里展示的更多内容吧!\\n&7[These are Mods that I've found perfect for decorating your house or base! \\n\\nFeel free to check out even more than what's shown here!]&f"]
	quest.3ED8365BAD406CC5.title: "装饰模组!&7[Decor Mods!]&f"
	quest.3EEF17C57375CC39.quest_desc: ["&l&a简易光源&f&r 添加了制作非常简单且易于使用的光源.\\n\\n当反转时,它们无需红石即可工作,并在红石信号激活时关闭.\\n\\n它有多种不同的颜色和形状!\\n&7[lSimply Lights adds very simple to make and easy to use lights.\\n\\nWhen inverted they will work without Redstone and will turn off when the Redstone signal goes activates it.\\n\\nThere are plenty of different colors and shapes of it!]&f"]
	quest.3EEF17C57375CC39.title: "&l&a简易光源&f&r&7[lSimply Light]&f"
	quest.3F185554793CCE54.quest_desc: ["要建造,你需要工具.而且你会想要工具.\\n\\n能帮你获取方块的工具,帮你获取这些方块不同版本的工具,以及帮你放置方块的工具!\\n\\n你需要从一根木棍开始!\\n&7[To build you will need Tools. And you will want Tools. \\n\\nTools that can help you get Blocks, Tools to help you get different versions of those Blocks, and Tools to help you place Blocks! \\n\\nYou'll need to start with a Stick!]&f"]
	quest.3F185554793CCE54.title: "工具!&7[Tools!]&f"
	quest.3FD9DC6B7844A79C.quest_desc: ["我一直讨厌混凝土是多么无聊,尤其是在现实生活中.\\n\\n好吧,至少在 &2&lMinecraft&r 中,有了 &l&bChipped&r 模组,我们可以获得不同的设计!\\n&7[I've always hated how boring Concrete is, especially in real life. \\n\\nWell atleast in lMinecraft with the lChipped Mod we can get different designs with it!]&f"]
	quest.3FD9DC6B7844A79C.title: "&l&bChipped&r 混凝土&7[lChipped Concrete]&f"
	quest.40C068B2B8AC0F33.quest_desc: ["地形改造是即使是最简单建筑的重要组成部分.但我们 &2&lMinecraft&r 玩家就是没有时间或精力去做.\\n\\n那么,为什么不让机器为我们做呢？\\n\\n采石场是非常简单的方法,但它们都始于方块破坏器.&a简易&f 方块破坏器只会破坏它前面的东西,不是很有帮助……\\n\\n但高级方块破坏器会开采一个设定的区域!这对地形改造来说好多了!\\n&7[Terraforming is an important part to even the simplest of Builds. But we lMinecraft Players just simply don't have the time or effort to do so. \\n\\nSo why not let Machines do it for us? \\n\\nQuarries are very easy ways of doing so but they all start with Block Breakers. The Simple Block Breaker will only break what is in front of it, not the most helpful... \\n\\nBut the Advanced Block Breaker will Mine a set Area! Much better for Terraforming!]&f"]
	quest.40C068B2B8AC0F33.title: "采石场与矿场&7[Quarries and Mines]&f"
	quest.44688FC2E34FF09F.quest_desc: ["Minecraft 已经添加了数百种方块,模组又添加了数百种!但有时这仍然不够.\\n\\n通过一些模组,我们可以将已有的方块改变成具有不同形状、设计,甚至变成全新的方块!\\n&7[Minecraft already adds hundreds of Blocks, and Mods add hundreds more! But sometimes it is still not enough. \\n\\nWith some Mods we can change the Blocks we already have into ones with different shapes, designs, and even into entirely new Blocks!]&f"]
	quest.44688FC2E34FF09F.title: "改变方块&7[Changing Blocks]&f"
	quest.48971CE964CF037F.quest_desc: ["虽然保护我们的 &a核反应堆&f 很重要,查看其内容物也与其安全相关.\\n\\n这种玻璃也可以用来让我们的基地看起来更漂亮!\\n\\n说真的,什么更重要:我们核反应堆的安全和保护？还是让我们的基地看起来更漂亮!\\n&7[While protecting our Nuclear Reactors are important and viewing the contents of them relate to the safety of it. \\n\\nThe Glass can also be used to make our bases look better! \\n\\nAnd really what's more important: safety and protection of our nuclear reactors? Or making our bases look better!]&f"]
	quest.4B552E9D05FF5415.quest_desc: ["&l&9X&cy&aC&8r&a&cf&9t&r 的核心就是那 5 种不同的颜色,这包括将它们用于方块!\\n\\n&a绿色&r、&c红色&r、&9蓝色&r、&8深色&r,以及各种各样的 &a泛光灯&f!\\n&7[lXyCraft is all about the 5 different Colors, this includes using them for Blocks! \\n\\nGreen, Red, Blue, Dark, and Light Blocks of all sorts!]&f"]
	quest.4B552E9D05FF5415.title: "&l&9X&cy&aC&8r&a&cf&9t&r &l世界&7[lXyCraft lWorld]&f"
	quest.55160BAFFD9E2988.quest_desc: ["典型的 &9Macaw&r 模组,&9&lMacaw's Furniture&r!\\n\\n它添加了你需要的一切!椅子、桌子、书架,甚至抽屉!\\n&7[The quintessential Macaw Mod, lMacaw's Furniture! \\n\\nIt adds everything you need! Chairs, Tables, Bookshelves, and even Drawers!]&f"]
	quest.55160BAFFD9E2988.title: "&l&9Macaw 的家具&r&7[lMacaw's Furniture]&f"
	quest.5716E84828EC0C23.quest_desc: ["塑料建筑砖是通过 &l&7&d气动工艺:重置版&f&r 制作的方块.\\n\\n就像它们现实生活中的对应物一样,踩上去很疼!\\n\\n所以要么穿上鞋子,要么把砖块磨平.\\n&7[Plastic Construction Bricks are Blocks made through lPneumaticCraft: Repressurized. \\n\\nJust like their real life counter parts they hurt to step on! \\n\\nSo either wear Shoes or smooth down the Bricks.]&f"]
	quest.5716E84828EC0C23.title: "塑料建筑砖&7[Plastic Construction Bricks]&f"
	quest.59B6C6BF0550D13D.quest_desc: ["新型玻璃,可用于你的火车!或者基地,\\n\\n我不能强迫你把它用于任何特定用途.\\n&7[New types of Glass that can be used with your Trains! Or bases, \\n\\nI can't make you use it for anything specific.]&f"]
	quest.59B6C6BF0550D13D.title: "&7&l&d铁路&f&r 玻璃&7[lRailcraft Glass]&f"
	quest.5AD09CCEEDC0B50F.quest_desc: ["这些真的超级有用,你绝对应该看看它们!\\n\\n真正的 &a光源&f 是 &a狂野闪耀之灯&f.它会在其周围大约 20 格或更远的范围内放置隐形的 &a光源&f.\\n\\n&a巨型火把&f 则不同:它不发光,但它能阻止 64 格范围内的所有敌对生物生成!这对使用 &a夜视&f 的人很有用.\\n\\n&a恐惧之灯&f 则相反,它阻止同一区域内的被动生物生成.\\n&7[Now these are super helpful, you should definitely check them out! \\n\\nThe actual Light Source is the Feral Flare Lantern. It will place invisible Light Sources around 20 Blocks or more around it. \\n\\nThe Mega Torch is different: it doesn't emit Light but it does Block all Hostile Mob spawns with 64 Blocks of it! Useful for those using Night Vision. \\n\\nThe Dread Lamp does the opposite, it blocks Passive Mob spawns in the same area.]&f"]
	quest.5AD09CCEEDC0B50F.title: "&l&e火炬大师&r&7[lTorchmaster]&f"
	quest.5C0588F5B9B65AFD.quest_desc: [
		"&d&lCamol&r 是伪装 &l一切&r 的答案.从 Pipez 到 &d通用机械&f 线缆,再到 &aATM之星&f,以及除了——不,等等,还有 &a厨房水槽&f 之外的一切.\\n&7[lCamol is the answer to camouflaging lEVERYTHING. From Pipez to Mekanism Cables to ATM Stars, and everything but the- no, wait, the Kitchen Sink, too.]&f"
		""
		"将 &d&l伪装方块&r 与你想要用于伪装的方块一起合成,然后 &a右击&f 你想要伪装的方块,比如某种线缆之类的.\\n&7[Craft the lCamo Block together with the block you want to use for the camo, then right click it on the block you want to camouflage, like some kind of cable or something.]&f"
		""
		"默认情况下,&d&l伪装方块&r 会采用被伪装方块的碰撞箱形状.你可以通过将其单独放入合成网格中来更改为保持形状的版本.这将使其采用伪装方块的形状.\\n&7[By default the lCamo Block will take on the collision shape of the camoed block. You can change this to the Shape Retaining version by putting it into a crafting grid by itself. This will make it take on the shape of the camoing block.]&f"
		""
		"如果你想 &a移除&f 一个 &d&l伪装方块&r,用另一个伪装方块 &a右击&f 被伪装的方块.\\n&7[If you want to remove a lCamo Block, right click the camoed block with another Camo Block.]&f"
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/building_tips/camol_example.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5C0588F5B9B65AFD.title: "&d&l卡莫尔&r&7[lCamol]&f"
	quest.5D5563142917495A.quest_desc: ["&l&eFarmer's Delight&r 全是关于耕种和烹饪 &a食物&f 的!我们也可以使用那些相同的物品进行装饰和使用!\\n\\n炉灶、锅和煎锅非常适合厨房.\\n\\n&a饲料桶&f 非常适合食品储藏室.\\n\\n农场物品非常适合户外装饰,而橱柜则适合任何地方!\\n&7[lFarmer's Delight is all about Farming and Cooking Food Items! We can also use those same Items for Decoration and usage! \\n\\nThe Stove, Pots, and Pans are perfect for a Kitchen. \\n\\nThe Food Barrels are great for a Pantry. \\n\\nThe Farm stuff is great for outdoor decor and the Cabinets are perfect for anywhere!]&f"]
	quest.5D5563142917495A.title: "&l&e农夫乐事&r&7[lFarmer's Delight]&f"
	quest.5E5D5D28D82F6891.quest_desc: ["&l&9X&cy&aC&8r&a&cf&9t&r 通过其 &l世界核心&r 添加了大量玻璃!\\n\\n从你可以穿过的,到发光的,再到更坚固的!\\n&7[lXyCraft adds plenty of Glasses with it's lWorld Core! \\n\\nFrom ones you can walk through, to glowing ones, to stronger ones!]&f"]
	quest.5E5D5D28D82F6891.title: "&l&9X&cy&aC&8r&a&cf&9t&r 玻璃&7[lXyCraft Glass]&f"
	quest.5EB488C393B084C4.quest_desc: ["A continuation of lChiseled, lRechiseled! \\n\\nAll of this Mod works within the Chisel Tool, Right Click with it to pull up its GUI. \\nOn the Left is where you choose the design and the Bottom Right is where you put the Blocks. \\n\\nAbove it you can view the design in set patterns: just the 1 Block, 3x1 Blocks, or 3x3 Wall of that Block. You can also set the image to either spin or not spin by clicking the button! \\n\\nNext to where the Blocks go, you can click the Chisel, doing this will set the selected design, to every Block in your Inventory that can be changed. \\n\\nAlso does not have Durability!"]
	quest.5EB488C393B084C4.title: "&4&l重塑凿刻&r&7[lRechiseled]&f"
	quest.5F7F753FD72BFBBF.quest_desc: ["&l&7&d铁路&f&r 添加了更多方块？我开始怀疑它到底是不是关于火车的了!\\n&7[More Blocks added by lRailcraft? I'm starting to doubt if it's even about Trains!]&f"]
	quest.5F7F753FD72BFBBF.title: "&l&7&d铁路&f&r 彩色方块&7[lRailcraft Colored Blocks]&f"
	quest.616ED6C49C37EB91.quest_desc: ["&b&lPaths and Pathways&r 添加了大量类似地毯的方块(以及完整的方块和台阶版本).\\n\\n这些显然被用作路径,它们看起来比 &2&lMinecraft&r 的路径方块漂亮多了.\\n&7[lPaths and Pathways adds tons of different Carpet like Blocks (and full Blocks and Slab versions). \\n\\nThese are obviously used as Paths, they just look much nicer than the lMinecraft Path Block. ]&f"]
	quest.616ED6C49C37EB91.title: "&b&lMacaw 的小径与铺路&7[lMacaw's Paths and Pavings]&f"
	quest.61BE7882EE0E6FAF.quest_desc: ["什么滚下楼梯 \\n独自或成双成对…… \\n滚过邻居的狗 \\n什么作为零食很棒 \\n还能背在背上？ \\n是原木!原木!原木!\\n&7[What rolls down stairs \\nAlone or in pairs... \\nRolls over your neighbor's dog \\nWhat's great for a snack \\nAnd fits on your back? \\nIt's Log! Log! Log!]&f"]
	quest.6258F26293B9C1C1.quest_desc: ["你问 &9&lCrystalix&r 给了我们什么？\\n它给了玻璃!所有不同类型的玻璃!有普通、清晰和有边框的.\\n\\n有边框的是正常的 &2&lMinecraft&r 玻璃图案.它有边框和角落附近的像素点,让你知道它是玻璃.清晰的玻璃有边框,但角落附近没有像素点,所以内部是完全清晰的.普通的玻璃没有边框或像素点,它是 100% 完全透明且单一颜色的.\\n\\n每种 &9&lCrystalix&r 玻璃也有自己的属性:无阴影、强化、光照和幽灵.\\n\\n无阴影会影响它对光影甚至 &2&lMinecraft&r 光照的反应.强化会影响 &a防爆强化大板&f.光照会影响它是发光、忽略光照,还是像普通玻璃一样让光照进来.幽灵可以改变谁能穿过玻璃,这个属性有最多的设置.\\n&7[What does lCrystalix give us you ask? \\nIt gives Glass! All different types of Glass! There is Normal, Clear, and Bordered. \\n\\nBordered is the normal lMinecraft Glass pattern. It has borders and pixels near corner to let you know it is Glass. Clear has the borders but no pixels near the corners, so the inside is all clear. Normal has no borders or pixels, it is entirely 100% clear and one color. \\n\\nEach lCrystalix Glass has its own properties as well: Shadeless, Reinforced, Light, and Ghost. \\n\\nShadeless will affect how it reacts to Shaders and even lMinecraft lighting. Reinforced will affect Blast Resistance. Light will affect whether it gives Light, ignores Light, or acts like normal Glass, letting Light in. Ghost will be able to change who can walk through the Glass, this one has the most settings.]&f"]
	quest.6258F26293B9C1C1.title: "&9&l水晶工艺&r&7[lCrystalix]&f"
	quest.6607E5CDB3D17D67.quest_desc: ["别担心,这些不会着火!\\n&7[Don't worry, these won't set on fire!]&f"]
	quest.6607E5CDB3D17D67.title: "&l&bChipped&r 羊毛&7[lChipped Wool]&f"
	quest.667CD7C6E87A05F4.quest_desc: ["&l&9X&cy&aC&8r&a&cf&9t&r 当然,由于涉及所有颜色,其灯光也基于颜色.\\n\\nRGB 灯的颜色取决于制作它们所用的染料.\\n\\n是染料,不是宝石.\\n&7[lXyCraft of course with being all around Colors, the Lights are also based on Color. \\n\\nThe RGB Lights will be whatever Dye they are made with. \\n\\nThe Dye specifically not the Gem.]&f"]
	quest.667CD7C6E87A05F4.title: "&l&9X&cy&aC&8r&a&cf&9t&r 光源&7[lXyCraft Lights]&f"
	quest.6AC85C203E7C3482.quest_desc: ["你从 &b&lMacaw's Mods&r 中每样都得到了一个.我想这是你应得的.\\n\\n我的意思是,你自己的 &bMacaw&r!\\n&7[You got one of everything from lMacaw's Mods. I think you've earned it. \\n\\nAnd by it I mean you're own Macaw!]&f"]
	quest.6AC85C203E7C3482.title: "完成 &bMacaw&r&7[Completed Macaw]&f"
	quest.6BC78AF7C9D93F11.quest_desc: ["甚至还有上釉的版本!\\n&7[Even Glazed versions!]&f"]
	quest.6BC78AF7C9D93F11.title: "&l&bChipped&r 陶瓦&7[lChipped Terracotta]&f"
	quest.6F65216B13E9FFA9.quest_desc: ["获取一个方块.字面意义上的任何方块.\\n\\n每个玩家都应该知道方块是建筑的基石.要真正建造点什么,你将需要方块.\\n&7[Get a Block. Literally any Block. \\n\\nEvery Player should know Blocks are the building Blocks of building. To actually build something you will need Blocks.]&f"]
	quest.6F65216B13E9FFA9.title: "方块!&7[Blocks!]&f"
	quest.72DB967E59EEA729.quest_desc: ["&3&lGlassential&r 是对建筑非常重要的模组,即使对于有特定用途的建筑也是如此!\\n它不仅仅是普通的玻璃,这些玻璃具有能力,可以在悬停在物品上时阅读!\\n\\n比如 &a缥缈玻璃&f,你可以穿过但怪物不能.(我在 9sky 的蜜蜂穹顶里用过那个!)\\n&7[lGlassential is very important Mod for building, even for builds with purposes! \\nIt's not just normal Glass, these have abilities which can be read while hovering over the Item! \\n\\nLike Ethereal Glass which you can walk through but Mobs can't. (I used that for my Bee Dome in 9sky!)]&f"]
	quest.72DB967E59EEA729.title: "&3&l玻璃工艺&r&7[lGlassential]&f"
	quest.7C2ED69E07988DF4.quest_desc: ["原版 &2&lMinecraft&r 的椅子,楼梯.\\n\\n欢迎来到模组 &2&lMinecraft&r,我们拥有的装饰品远不止楼梯.\\n\\n有几十个模组添加了装饰品,甚至还有更多模组添加了可用于装饰的物品!\\n&7[The original lMinecraft Chair, the stairs. \\n\\nWelcome to Modded lMinecraft, we have much more than just stairs for decoration. \\n\\nThere are dozens of mods that add decoration and even more that add items that can be used for decoration!]&f"]
	quest.7C2ED69E07988DF4.title: "装饰!&7[Decoration!]&f"
	quest.7CF13A4941F608E5.quest_desc: ["从普通玻璃,到带窗格的玻璃,甚至马赛克玻璃!\\n&7[From normal Glass, to Glass with Panes, to even Mosaics!]&f"]
	quest.7CF13A4941F608E5.title: "&l&bChipped&r 玻璃&7[lChipped Glass]&f"
	quest.7DA8ACE06DE8097F.quest_desc: ["&6铜&r 是 &2&lMinecraft&r 中最丰富的矿石,其主要用途是装饰.\\n\\n&2&lMinecraft&r 已经添加了许多不同的变种,但 &l&bChipped&r 认为这还不够好!所以我们得到了更多!\\n\\n甚至还有氧化版本的变种.\\n\\n你可以制作仿制的 &a绿宝石块&r.\\n&7[Copper is the most abundant Ore in lMinecraft and its main use is for decoration. \\n\\nThere's already plenty of different variants added by lMinecraft but lChipped didn't think it was good enough! So we got more! \\n\\nEven variants for the oxidized versions. \\n\\nYou can make faux Emerald Blocks.]&f"]
	quest.7DA8ACE06DE8097F.title: "&l&bChipped &6铜&7[lChipped Copper]&f"
	quest.7DABD82393713B5A.quest_desc: ["&c&lLuminax&r 是一个非常简单的模组.你喜欢彩色灯光吗？你可以拥有彩色灯光.\\n\\n它们都是单一颜色,没有纹理,并且可以有不同形状,如楼梯、台阶,甚至是 &a压力板&f!\\n\\n它们甚至能与 &l&cDy&6en&e&ami&bcs&r 一起工作!\\n&7[lLuminax is a very simple Mod. You like Colored Lights? You can have Colored Lights. \\n\\nThey are all one color with no Texturing and can come in different Shapes like Stairs or Slabs or even Pressure Plates! \\n\\nThey even work with lDyenamics!]&f"]
	quest.7DABD82393713B5A.title: "&l&c流明工艺&r&7[lLuminax]&f"
	quest.7E49C985A0433B20.quest_desc: ["&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r 是一个非常有趣的魔法模组,并带来了它自己的一套木材!\\n\\n秘术木有 5 种不同颜色的树木,它们生成在大多数生物群系中,但主要在其秘术木生物群系中!\\n&7[lArs Nouveau is a very fun magic Mod and with it brings its own set of Wood! \\n\\nArchwood comes in 5 different colors of trees that spawn in most Biomes but mostly in their Archwood Biome!]&f"]
	quest.7E49C985A0433B20.title: "&d&l&d新生魔艺&f&r 原木&7[lArs Nouveau Logs]&f"
