	task.7213278CEE1B25A3.title: "原木&7[Logs]&f"
	task.74CA4DE423248784.title: "&a壁灯&f&7[Wall Lamps]&f"
	task.76C92D826994D92B.title: "Chipped玻璃&7[Chipped Glass]&f"
	task.773B7F8C77B21B28.title: "Chipped羊毛&7[Chipped Wool]&f"
	task.78ECC6C98CA985D7.title: "Macaw的栅栏与墙&7[Macaw's Fences and Walls]&f"
	task.79400615E3A7401D.title: "&d建筑小帮手&f&7[Building Gadgets]&f"
	quest.01B5005BF9056A2E.quest_subtitle: "锤击沙子&7[Hammer Sand]&f"
	quest.040C336C718DCC7D.quest_desc: ["这是一个&6&lATM整合包&r,你将需要&l大量&r的材料.\\n\\n那么,我们该如何处理成吨的&7沙砾&r呢？就用无数个箱子装起来吗？\\n\\n不,我们可以将9个方块合成1个压缩方块.\\n\\n这适用于许多不同的方块,并且每个都可以被进一步压缩!\\n&7[This is an lATM Modpack, you'll need lLOTS of Materials. \\n\\nSo what will we do with our tons of Gravel? Just use a billion Chests? \\n\\nNo, instead we can combine 9 Blocks into 1 Compressed Block. \\n\\nThis works with a ton of different Blocks and each can be Compressed even further!]&f"]
	quest.040C336C718DCC7D.title: "压缩方块&7[Compressed Blocks]&f"
	quest.043AB8772206FF71.quest_desc: ["&0燧石&r可以通过像平常一样破坏&7沙砾&r小概率获得,或者通过&b筛&r方块获得!\\n\\n通常在&2&lMinecraft&r里&0燧石&r相当没用.做成&a打火石&f然后……就没别的了.\\n\\n但&b&l空岛&r就大不相同了!所以在游戏初期要收集并保存好它.\\n&7[Flint can be gained rarely from Breaking Gravel like normal, or from Sieving Blocks! \\n\\nUsually Flint is pretty garbage in lMinecraft. Makes Flint and Steel then... nothing else. \\n\\nlSkyblock is much different though! So grab and save it for the early game.]&f"]
	quest.043AB8772206FF71.title: "&8燧石&7[Flint]&f"
	quest.04ACC7E762537FB4.quest_desc: ["我们不需要无数台花哨的机器来复制矿石……我们只需要几台!\\n\\n来自&3&lID&r的&3&l挤压机&r可以将&7粗矿块&r变成&7粗矿&r.\\n\\n要使用它,只需将&7粗矿块&r放入&3&l挤压机&r,然后跳上去将其压下.一旦它被压碎,&7粗矿&r就会被吐出.偶尔它甚至可能给出更多!\\n\\n但是等等!还没完!\\n\\n我们还有矿石锤,这些锤子可以将&7&a粗矿&f&r敲成2份&7矿粉&r,而矿粉&a可被熔炉烧制&f成&7锭&r.\\n&7[We won't need a billion fancy Machines to Dupe Ores here... we'll only need a few! \\n\\nThe lSqueezer from lID can turn Raw Ore Blocks into Raw Ore. \\n\\nIn order to use it, just place the Raw Ore Block into the lSqueezer and Jump on it to push it downward. Once it is Crushed, the Raw Ore will be spit out. Rarely it might give even more! \\n\\nBut wait! That's not all! \\n\\nWe also have Ore Hammers, these can crack Raw Ores into 2 Dust, which can be Smelted into Ingots.]&f"]
	quest.04ACC7E762537FB4.title: "简易矿石复制&7[Easy Ore Duping]&f"
	quest.091F1D752FA3BAAC.quest_desc: ["只需要2个&0燧石&r,我们就能制作&0燧石剪刀&r.它们的功能和剪刀一样,只是更便宜.\\n\\n我们需要它们来获取&2树叶&r!\\n\\n还有羊毛……如果你需要羊毛的话.\\n&7[With just 2 Flint we can make Flint Shears. They work just like Shears, just cheaper. \\n\\nWe'll need them to get Leaves! \\n\\nAnd Wool... if you need Wool.]&f"]
	quest.091F1D752FA3BAAC.title: "收集&2树叶&7[Collecting Leaves]&f"
	quest.0BD70DFE33D84323.quest_desc: [
		"&b&l筛子&r是我们获取大部分资源的方式.\\n\\n把它们放下来,它们不会做太多事.我们需要给它们一个筛网才能使用.&a线&r筛网是第一个,但它可以升级.\\n\\n只需用筛网&a右击&b&l筛子&r即可放置,按住Shift&a右击&r即可取出.\\n\\n放入筛网后,我们现在可以将某些方块&a右击&r放入&b&l筛子&r来筛它们.持续&a右击&r或&a等一下&r,一旦它们完全通过,就会掉落物品.\\n\\n专业提示:如果&b&l筛子&r彼此相邻,它们会同时工作!这最多可以覆盖一个5x5的区域!\\n&7[lSieves are how we will get most of our Resources. \\n\\nPlace them down and they won't do much. We'll need to give them a Mesh in order to use them. The String Mesh is the first one but it can be upgraded. \\n\\nJust Right Click the lSieve with a Mesh to place it and Shift Right Click it to take it out. \\n\\nWith the Mesh in, we can now Right Click certain Blocks into the lSieve to push them through. Keep Right Clicking or Hold it and once they are all the way they will Drop Items. \\n\\nPro Tip: if there is lSieves next to each other, they were work at the same time! This goes up to a 5x5 area!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_sieve.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_sieves.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0BD70DFE33D84323.title: "&b&l筛子&r与筛网&7[lSieves and Meshes]&f"
	quest.0D794D25F04E04A7.quest_desc: ["我们在&c&l&a地狱&f&r里无法获得&4下界岩&r.那里有点空.相反,我们需要制作一些!\\n\\n在&6&l木桶&r中将&5&a巫水&f&r与&c熔岩&r混合来制作&4下界岩&r.\\n\\n我们也可以用&8锤子&r敲碎它,然后&b筛&r碎块以获得更多物品!\\n&7[We can't get Netherrack in lThe Nether. It is kinda empty. Instead we'll need to make some! \\n\\nCombine Witch Water with Lava in a lBarrel to make Netherrack. \\n\\nWe can also Crush it with a Hammer to Sieve it for more Items!]&f"]
	quest.0D794D25F04E04A7.title: "&4下界岩&7[Netherrack]&f"
	quest.0E7F7CF44A982EA3.quest_desc: ["&7黏土球&r和骨粉可以制作&3&a瓷土&f&r.\\n\\n这将用于制作&3桶&r或更大的桶,称为&c&l坩埚&r!\\n&7[Clay Balls and Bonemeal can make Porcelain Clay. \\n\\nThis will be needed for making Buckets or bigger Buckets called lCrucibles!]&f"]
	quest.0E7F7CF44A982EA3.title: "&3&a瓷土&f&7[Porcelain Clay]&f"
	quest.0FEFD055B435B17F.quest_desc: ["现在我们终于可以获取一些&c熔岩&r了.再也不用担心搞砸&7&a圆石制造机&f&r了!\\n\\n我们无法制作无限的&c熔岩源&r,但至少我们可以持续制造更多.\\n\\n它对于&a流体混合&r和其他配方非常重要,所以你可能会需要很多!\\n&7[Now we can finally get some Lava. Don't worry about screwing up Cobble Generators anymore! \\n\\nWe can't make Infinite Lava Sources but atleast we can keep making more. \\n\\nIt is very important for Fluid Mixing and other Recipes so you'll probably need a ton of it!]&f"]
	quest.0FEFD055B435B17F.title: "&c熔岩&7[Lava]&f"
	quest.11032183CCCA206D.quest_desc: ["&a&a被动型生物&f&r需要两个条件才能生成.\\n\\n1. &2草方块&r,这个我们有.\\n\\n2. 光照,这个我们需要!\\n\\n如果光照足够,并且有&2草方块&r供它们生成,它们就会随机生成.\\n\\n有时可能需要一段时间才能生效.\\n&7[Passive Mobs need 2 things to Spawn. \\n\\n1. Grass, which we have. \\n\\n2. Light, which we will need! \\n\\nIf it is Light enough, with Grass for them to Spawn. They will randomly Spawn. \\n\\nIt can take awhile to work sometimes.]&f"]
	quest.11032183CCCA206D.title: "&a&a被动型生物&f&7[Passive Mobs]&f"
	quest.128A1EEAF8F45042.quest_desc: ["&5&a菌丝孢子&f&r很少从&b筛&r泥土中获得.\\n\\n它们的作用类似于&2&a草籽&f&r,将其放在泥土或&2草方块&r上以获得&5菌丝&r!\\n&7[Mycelium Spores come rarely from Sieving Dirt. \\n\\nThey work like Grass Seeds, place them on Dirt or Grass to get Mycelium!]&f"]
	quest.128A1EEAF8F45042.title: "霉菌来袭!&7[Bring on the Mold!]&f"
	quest.145917B219D0D28D.quest_desc: ["所有&b空岛&r世界都会生成必需品:&2草方块&r和一棵&2树&r.\\n\\n我们需要这棵&2树&r来获取&6木头&r以及所有由&6木头&r制成的东西.那&2草方块&r呢？\\n\\n嗯,原因有三:1. &a&a被动型生物&f&r需要&2草方块&r才能生成.2. &2草方块&r会向其他泥土蔓延.3. 我们可以按住Shift&a右击&2草方块&r来获取&7小石子&r!\\n&7[All Skyblock Worlds spawn with the necessities. Grass and a Tree. \\n\\nWe'll need the Tree for Wood and everything from Wood. What about Grass? \\n\\nWell for 1. Passive Mobs need Grass to Spawn. 2. Grass spreads to other Dirt. 3. We can Shift Right Click Grass for Pebbles!]&f"]
	quest.145917B219D0D28D.title: "&2草方块&7[Grass]&f"
	quest.162AB6F9257EB71E.quest_desc: [
		"有很多方法可以产生你最初的一点能量.\\n&7[There are plenty of ways to generate your first bits of power.]&f"
		""
		"在这个整合包中,Generators Galore 已经进行了全面改进!升级到8倍和64倍的成本更低,并且整体能量产量增加,给自己弄一些强大的熔岩发电机,然后开始吧!如果我们想在ATM10:TTS中开始自动化,我们需要进一步涉足能源和一些新模组!\\n&7[In this pack, Generators Galore has been given an overhaul! With cheaper upgrades to 8x and 64x, and increased energy production across the board, grab yourself some hefty lava gen, and get going!If we want to get started with automation in ATM10:TTS, we'll need to dip our toes further into power and some new mods!]&f"
		""
		"以下是它包含的一些模组!\\n&7[Here are some of the mods it includes!]&f"
		""
		"&bGenerators Galore&r(等级与改动)\\n&7[Generators Galore (tiers and changes)]&f"
		""
		"&b&a生长加速器&f等级&r(我们推荐定向的,它超级快!)\\n&7[Growth Accelerator tiers (we recommend directional, it's super fast!)]&f"
		""
		"&bGeores&r(种植你缺少的那些材料!)&r\\n&7[Geores (Grow those materials you are missing!)]&f"
	]
	quest.162AB6F9257EB71E.title: "下一篇章&7[The Next Chapter]&f"
	quest.1B186F14606C07D7.quest_desc: ["在&6&l木桶&r(希望是&7&l石头&r做的)中将&e荧石&r与&c熔岩&r混合,可以制作&e末地石&r.\\n\\n就像&4下界岩&r一样,我们可以用&8锤子&r敲碎它,然后&b筛&r碎块!\\n\\n这会给我们&3&a末影珍珠&f&r、&a末影之眼&r等等……\\n&7[Combining Glowstone with Lava in a lBarrel (hopefully a lStone one) will make Endstone. \\n\\nJust like Netherrack we can use a Hammer to Crush it and then Sieved the Crush parts! \\n\\nThis will give us Ender Pearls, Eyes of Ender, and more...]&f"]
	quest.1B186F14606C07D7.title: "&e末地石&7[End Stone]&f"
	quest.1E9F1FBAA6AAA43B.quest_desc: ["&c&a敌对性生物&f&r比&a被动型&r更容易生成.\\n\\n只要足够黑暗,并且它们距离你至少24格远,它们就会生成.\\n\\n如果你的岛屿变得更大,你可能需要把它照亮!\\n&7[Hostile Mobs are easier to Spawn then Passive. \\n\\nAs long as it is Dark enough, and they are atleast 24 Blocks away from you, they will Spawn. \\n\\nIf your Island is getting bigger, you might want to Light it up!]&f"]
	quest.1E9F1FBAA6AAA43B.title: "&c&a敌对性生物&f&7[Hostile Mobs]&f"
	quest.1FA3ACD9B8CD02FE.quest_desc: ["哪种&9水&r？&5&a巫水&f&r!\\n\\n在&5&a菌丝体块&f&r上方放置一个&6&l木桶&r,并在其中放入&9水&r以获得&5&a巫水&f&r.\\n这需要一点时间,但没关系,我们有耐心!\\n\\n(顺便说一下,任何靠近&5&a巫水&f&r的&5&a菌丝体块&f&r都会开始生长&c蘑菇&r!)\\n&7[Which Water? Witch Water! \\n\\nPlace a lBarrel above a Mycelium Block and place Water in it to get Witch Water. \\nIt takes a second but that's okay, we have patience! \\n\\n(BTW, any Mycelium Blocks near the Witch Water will begin growing Mushrooms!)]&f"]
	quest.1FA3ACD9B8CD02FE.title: "&5&a巫水&f&7[Witch Water]&f"
	quest.23E71537225B8392.quest_desc: [
		"有了我们新获得的木头,我们可以制作木棍.用我们的木棍,我们可以制作一个&6钩子&r!\\n\\n这些可以用来破坏&2树叶&r.当它们这样做时,&2树叶&r会掉落更多&2树苗&r和一个叫做&e蚕&r的新物品.\\n\\n把那些&e蚕&r扔到&2树叶&r上以感染它们.这会传播到其他树叶,并随着时间的推移而生长.\\n\\n你可能会问,哪个理智的人会想要&e蚕&r感染呢？\\n\\n当然是为了线!现在只需破坏那些白色的树叶就能得到它.\\n&7[With our new found Wood, we can make Sticks. With our Sticks we can make a Crook! \\n\\nThese can be used to Break Leaves. When they do, the Leaves will Drop more Saplings and a new Item called Silkworms. \\n\\nThrow those Silkworms on Leaves to Infest them. This will spread to other Leaves and grow over time. \\n\\nWhy would any sane person want a Silkworm Infestation you ask? \\n\\nFor String of course! Just Break those White Leaves now to get it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_tree.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.23E71537225B8392.title: "感染我们的&2树&7[Infesting our Trees]&f"
	quest.25B49E9D15BAEF3E.quest_desc: ["&9水&r可以通过几种不同的方式获得.\\n\\n&9雨&r、&6&l木桶&r堆肥、&b冰&r!\\n\\n无论你怎么做,都可以通过在2x2区域内斜对角放置2个&9水源&r来立即制作一个&9无限水源&r.\\n\\n现在我们再也不用担心获取&9水&r了!\\n&7[Water can come from a few different ways. \\n\\nRain, lBarrel Composting, Ice! \\n\\nHowever you do it, instantly make an Infinite Water Source by placing 2 Water Sources diagonal from each other in a 2x2 area. \\n\\nNow we won't have to worry about getting Water anymore!]&f"]
	quest.25B49E9D15BAEF3E.title: "&9水&7[Water]&f"
	quest.29F82373417B2006.quest_desc: ["树苗用完了？你可以在任务菜单的右上角获取一些紧急树苗!它也是可重复的:如果发生什么不好的事情,不需要重启你的世界!\\n&7[Ran out of saplings? You can get some emergency saplings at the top right of the quest menu! It's repeatable too: no need to restart your world if something bad happens!\",]&f"]
	quest.29F82373417B2006.title: "紧急树苗&7[Emergency Saplings]&f"
	quest.2A3BF8D20EEED292.quest_desc: [
		"&6&l(橡木)木桶&r与&2&lMinecraft&r的木桶大不相同.\\n\\n事实上,我们需要它来制作许多不同的物品和方块!\\n\\n我们可以通过在桶内放入液体,然后将物品丢入其中,来混合物品与液体.\\n\\n甚至可以通过将两种液体都放入&6&l木桶&r来进行液体混合.\\n\\n顺便说一下,与&c熔岩&r混合时,你应该使用&7&l&a石质桶&f&r.&6木头&r做的会烧起来!\\n\\n如果下雨,它会装满&9水&r.\\n&7[The l(Oak) Barrel is a whole lot different from lMinecraft Barrels. \\n\\nInfact we'll need it for lots of different Items and Blocks! \\n\\nWe can use it to Mix Items with Liquids by placing a Liquid inside and Dropping an Item into it. \\n\\nOr even Liquid Mixing by placing both of them into the lBarrel. \\n\\nBy the way, for Mixing with Lava you should use a lStone Barrel. Wood ones will Burn! \\n\\nIf there is Rain, it will fill up with Water.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_barrel.png width:100 height:110 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_leaves.png width:100 height:110 align:center}"
	]
	quest.2A3BF8D20EEED292.title: "&6&l(橡木)木桶&7[l(Oak) Barrel]&f"
	quest.2C134DDBF9283407.quest_desc: ["对于那些想要快速开始的人,这为你提供了一个”简单模式”的开局.你不必完成这个任务,它对进程是可选的.\\n&7[For those who want to fast-track the start, this gives you an 'easy-mode' start. You do not have to complete this quest, and it is optional for progression.]&f"]
	quest.2C134DDBF9283407.quest_subtitle: "对于那些想要跳过的人&7[For those who want to skip forward]&f"
	quest.2C134DDBF9283407.title: "抢先一步&7[A head Start]&f"
	quest.322F7A333B35F7FD.quest_desc: ["为了获取材料,我们需要通过 &b&l筛子&r 处理方块……好吧,但这些 &7岩石&r 太硬了,无法通过 &b&l筛子&r.\\n\\n不如我们用 &8锤子&r 把它们砸碎!\\n\\n你以为我在开玩笑吗？用 &8锤子&r 破坏方块,得到它们的粉碎版本!\\n&7[To get Materials we need to process Blocks through lSieves... okay but these Rocks are too hard to pass through the lSieve. \\n\\nHow about we Hammer them down! \\n\\nDid you think I was kidding? Break Blocks with the Hammer to get a Crushed down version of them!]&f"]
	quest.322F7A333B35F7FD.title: "&8锤子&7[Hammers]&f"
	quest.376BAC497511F067.quest_desc: [
		"如果你在工作台中用铁锭围住熔炉,就可以将熔炉升级为 &a铁熔炉&f.\\n&7[If you surround a furnace with Iron in a crafting table, you can upgrade your furnace to an Iron Furnace.]&f"
		""
		"它们熔炼速度更快,并且可以通过 GUI 左上角的齿轮轮进行配置以实现自动化.\\n&7[These smelt faster and can also be configured to be automated with the cogwheel in the top left of the GUI.]&f"
	]
	quest.376BAC497511F067.quest_subtitle: "这个整合包里的所有东西都能升级吗？&7[Does everything get an upgrade in this pack?]&f"
	quest.376BAC497511F067.title: "用铁熔炼铁&7[Smelting iron with iron]&f"
	quest.3948A052907BEC04.quest_subtitle: "锤击黑石&7[Hammer Blackstone]&f"
	quest.3C5AAFC9672F2CF7.quest_desc: ["我们也可以把泥土扔进 &b&l筛子&r 来获取物品!\\n\\n泥土相当稀有且必要,所以确保你有足够的泥土来 &b筛&r.\\n\\n泥土会给我们 &2作物&r 作为物品,以及 &2&a草籽&f&r!&2&a草籽&f&r 可以用于泥土来生成 &2草方块&r.\\n\\n任何泥土,任何地方!\\n&7[We can also throw Dirt into a lSieve to get Items! \\n\\nDirt is pretty rare and necessary so make sure you have enough to Sieve. \\n\\nDirt will give us Crops as an Item as well as Grass Seeds! Grass Seeds can be used on Dirt to make Grass. \\n\\nAny Dirt, anywhere!]&f"]
	quest.3C5AAFC9672F2CF7.title: "&2&a草籽&f&7[Grass Seeds]&f"
	quest.441200BE0C75C2AD.quest_desc: ["筛网可以升级!并且需要升级才能获得新物品!\\n\\n你可以查看 JEI 了解所有物品,但基本上筛网越好,物品掉落越好.\\n\\n物品掉落和掉落率都会随着筛网改变.\\n&7[Meshes can be upgraded! And will need to be upgraded in order to get new Items! \\n\\nYou can check JEI for all Items but basically the better the Mesh, the better Item Drops. \\n\\nItem Drops and Drop Rate both change with the Mesh.]&f"]
	quest.441200BE0C75C2AD.title: "&a增强&f 筛网&7[Upgraded Meshes]&f"
	quest.469E414BC7F0C238.quest_desc: ["&3瓷桶&r 的工作方式类似于 &7&a铁桶&f&r.\\n\\n只是更便宜,游戏前期更容易获得,并且在放置 &c熔岩&r 后会损坏!\\n\\n等等,什么？\\n\\n是的,它们不耐热,在你放置 &c熔岩&r 后,&3桶&r 会损坏.\\n\\n不过 &9水&r 没问题!\\n&7[Porcelain Buckets work like Iron Buckets. \\n\\nJust cheaper, easier to get early game, and break after placing Lava! \\n\\nWait what? \\n\\nYeah, they aren't good with the heat and after you place the Lava the Bucket wil break. \\n\\nWater is fine though!]&f"]
	quest.469E414BC7F0C238.title: "&3瓷桶&7[Porcelain Bucket]&f"
	quest.488C8BDF45B9CA0F.quest_desc: [
		"&a传送门&r 是获取 &a&a被动型生物&f&r 和 &a战利品奖励&f 的简单方法!\\n\\n好吧,也许并不简单.你需要击退一波波的 &c怪物&r.另外,你需要一个 &a&a末影之眼&f&r 来制作它.\\n\\n但这是值得的!\\n\\n不同的 &a传送门&r 给予不同的奖励和 &c怪物&r.这个会给予每种农场动物各 6 只.\\n&7[Gateways are easy ways to get Passive Mobs and Loot Rewards! \\n\\nOkay, maybe not easy. You'll need to Fight off Waves of Monsters. Plus you'll need an Eye of Ender to make it. \\n\\nBut it is worth it! \\n\\nDifferent Gates give different Rewards and Monsters. This one will give 6 of each Farm Animal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_gateway.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.488C8BDF45B9CA0F.title: "自由生物!!!&7[Free Mobs!!!]&f"
	quest.4C502B5A1C1A0C58.quest_desc: ["有了&5&a巫水&f&r,我们可以像从&9水&f&r中获得&7黏土&f&r一样,把&e沙子&f&r扔进去,只不过这次我们会得到&8&a灵魂沙&f&r.\\n\\n&8&a灵魂沙&f&r可以&b筛&f&r来获得更多&c&l下界&f&r物品!\\n\\n哦对了,你可能会对&c&l下界&f&r感到失望……\\n&7[With Witch Water we can toss Sand into it like how we get Clay from Water, just now we will get Soul Sand. \\n\\nSoul Sand can be Sieved to get more lNether Items! \\n\\nOh yeah, you might be disappointed by the lNether...]&f"]
	quest.4C502B5A1C1A0C58.title: "&8&a灵魂沙&f&7[Soul Sand]&f"
	quest.4CCA1C828677D518.quest_desc: ["按住Shift键并&a右击&f&2草方块&f&r的顶部,它会给你&7小石子&f&r!\\n\\n&7小石子&f&r对应&7石头&f&r、&8深板岩&f&r、&7安山岩&f&r、&d花岗岩&f&r、闪长岩、&0黑石&f&r和&8玄武岩&f&r.\\n\\n我们可以将4个&7小石子&f&r合成与&7小石子&f&r相关的&7石头&f&r.或者,只需在物品栏中将鼠标悬停在一堆&7小石子&f&r上并按K键!\\n\\n这对许多具有相似合成配方的物品都有效,试试看吧!\\n&7[By Holding Shift Right Click while looking at the Top of a Grass Block it will give Pebbles! \\n\\nPebbles for Stone, Deepslate, Andesite, Granite, Diorite, Blackstone, and Basalt. \\n\\nWe can combine 4 Pebbles to make the Stone related to the Pebbles. Or just Press K while hovering over a bunch of them in your Inventory! \\n\\nThat works for lots of Items with similar Recipes, try it out!]&f"]
	quest.4CCA1C828677D518.title: "挖掘&2草方块&7[Digging through Grass]&f"
	quest.522B2CE771DDBA0F.quest_desc: ["我撒谎了,&6&l木桶&f&r不仅能混合液体和流体.它们还能堆肥!\\n\\n把一些&2作物&f&r、&2苔藓&f&r或&2树叶&f&r扔进一个&6&l(橡木)桶&f&r,它就会变成泥土.\\n\\n这是前期获得更多泥土的唯一方法!\\n&7[I lied, lBarrels don't just Mix Liquids and Fluids. They also Compost! \\n\\nThrow some Crops, Moss, or Leaves into a l(Oak) Barrel and it will turn into Dirt. \\n\\nThis is the only early game way of getting more Dirt!]&f"]
	quest.522B2CE771DDBA0F.title: "制造泥土？&7[Making Dirt?]&f"
	quest.52DD11BC71F45E32.quest_desc: [
		"&9&l炼药锅&f&r在这里只有一个原因.非免费的&9水&f&r!\\n\\n你可以等待&9雨&f&r免费填满&6木桶&f&r,或者直接把&2树叶&f&r扔进&9&l炼药锅&f&r里等待.\\n\\n相信我,&9&l炼药锅&f&r要快得多!\\n&7[lCrucibles are only here for one reason. Non-free Water! \\n\\nYou can wait for Rain to fill Barrels for free or just throw Leaves into a lCrucible and wait. \\n\\nTrust me the lCrucible is much quicker!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_crucible.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.52DD11BC71F45E32.title: "从&2树叶&f&r获取&9水&7[Water from Leaves]&f"
	quest.60D53C6A50F9245B.quest_subtitle: "锤击沙砾&7[Hammer Gravel]&f"
	quest.6113DCE514DBB5D4.quest_subtitle: "锤击圆石&7[Hammer Cobble]&f"
	quest.62AF24DD96B7B4AD.quest_desc: ["当我们&b&l筛&f&r&7矿石&f&r时,不会得到完整的&7粗矿&f&r.不,那太简单了!我们得到的是&7矿石块&f&r!\\n\\n4个&7矿石块&f&r可以合成1个&7粗矿块&f&r.\\n\\n你可以在物品栏中将鼠标悬停在&7矿石块&f&r上按K键来立即合成它们!\\n&7[When we lSieve for Ores we won't get the full Raw Ore. No, that's too easy! We get Chunks! \\n\\n4 Chunks will make 1 Raw Ore Block. \\n\\nYou can use K while hovering over the Chunks in your Inventory to combine them instantly!]&f"]
	quest.62AF24DD96B7B4AD.title: "&7&a矿石碎块&f&7[Ore Chunks]&f"
	quest.62C9E87ECD00CA84.quest_desc: ["&b&l空岛&f&r开始时和任何普通的&2&lMinecraft&f&r世界一样!敲打那棵&2树&f&r!\\n\\n只是……别往下看.\\n\\n小心别弄丢了&2树苗&f&r!\\n&7[lSkyblock starts out like any normal lMinecraft World! Smack that Tree! \\n\\nJust... don't look down. \\n\\nAnd careful not to lose the Sapling! ]&f"]
	quest.62C9E87ECD00CA84.title: "空手撸&2树&7[Punching Trees]&f"
	quest.62FCB337688ACDBC.quest_desc: ["甚至不用担心制作&6木制工具&f&r,直接去弄&7石头&f&r.\\n\\n是的,你仍然可以用&9水&f&r和&c熔岩&f&r制作&7&l&a石制发电机&f&r!\\n\\n如果你选择更难的路线,你现在还不能用那些.你需要更多地跟随任务才能到达那里.\\n&7[Don't even worry about making Wooden Tools just go straight to Stone. \\n\\nAnd yes, you can still make lStone Generators with Water and Lava! \\n\\nIf you're taking the harder route, you can't use those just yet. You'll need to follow the Quests more to get there.]&f"]
	quest.62FCB337688ACDBC.title: "&7圆石&7[Cobblestone]&f"
	quest.647E94E2156CB596.quest_desc: [
		"如果你玩过&b&lATM9TTS&f&r,你可能还记得&7&a石制发电机&f&r方块,它会在它上方的物品栏中生成&7圆石&f&r.\\n\\n这些工作方式有点不同……你仍然需要在&7&l发电机&f&r上方有一个物品栏来收集方块,但它的工作方式不同.\\n\\n为了工作,我们需要在&7&l发电机&f&r的两个侧面各有一个&c熔岩源&f&r和&9水源&f&r.然后,它就会开始制造&7圆石&f&r.\\n\\n如果我们想制造其他方块,比如&7安山岩&f&r甚至&5黑曜石&f&r,我们需要把这些方块放在&7&l发电机&f&r下面.查看JEI以查看更多配方!\\n\\n我们可以升级&l&7发电机&f&r,这些只会加快它们的速度!\\n&7[If you've played lATM9TTS you probably remember Stone Generator Blocks that would just make Cobble in an Inventory above it. \\n\\nThese work a bit differently... you'll still need an Inventory above the lGenerator to collect the Blocks but the way it works is different. \\n\\nIn order to work we'll need a Lava Source and Water Source on 2 of the Sides of the lGenerator. Then, it will start making Cobble. \\n\\nIf we want to make other Blocks like Andesite or even Obsidian, we'll need to place those Blocks under the lGenerator. Check JEI to see more Recipes! \\n\\nWe can upgrade the lGenerators, these will just Speed them up!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_stone.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.647E94E2156CB596.title: "&7&l&a石制发电机&f&7[lStone Generator]&f"
	quest.658751C690E2B520.quest_subtitle: "锤击深板岩&7[Hammer Deepslate]&f"
	quest.6C1D268CE2B0D05D.quest_desc: [
		"烧制一些&3瓷土&f&r制成一个&c&l瓷坩埚&f&r.\\n\\n它们有一个目的.将物品烧制成&c熔岩&f&r!\\n\\n把&c&l坩埚&f&r放在一个&6&a热源&f&r上方.一些&6热量&f&r会加速这个过程.&c火&f&r比&e灯笼&f&r效果更好,&c熔岩&f&r比&c火&f&r效果更好.\\n\\n然后,把方块放进&c&l坩埚&f&r里.比如&7石头&f&r甚至&4下界岩&f&r.过一段时间,它就会制造出&c熔岩&f&r!\\n&7[Cook up some Porcelain into a lPorcelain Crucible. \\n\\nThese have 1 purpose. Cooking Items into Lava! \\n\\nThrow the lCrucible above a Heat Source. Some Heat more which Speed up the process. Fire does more than Lanterns, Lava does more than Fire. \\n\\nThen, place Blocks into the lCrucible. Like Stone or even Netherrack. After some time it will make Lava!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap1/chap1_lava.png width:120 height:200 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6C1D268CE2B0D05D.title: "&c&l瓷坩埚&7[lPorcelain Crucible]&f"
	quest.6CCF2126B2BA72A6.quest_desc: ["通常我们在&2&a繁茂洞穴&f&r里找到&2苔藓&f&r……呃,&b&l天空&f&r里的洞穴在哪里？\\n\\n好吧,我们总是可以把4个&2&a草籽&f&r合成1个&2苔藓&f&r!\\n\\n这听起来不像公平交易？你忘了你可以用骨粉催熟&2苔藓&f&r,让它蔓延到附近所有的泥土、&2草方块&f&r和&7石头&f&r上吗？\\n\\n&2苔藓&f&r可以像泥土一样被&b筛&f&r,但我们得到的不是&2作物&f&r,而是&2树苗&f&r!\\n&7[Usually we find Moss in Lush Caves... ummm where are Caves in the lSky? \\n\\nWell we can always just combine 4 Grass Seeds to make 1 Moss! \\n\\nThat doesn't sound like a fair trade? Did you forget you can Bonemeal Moss to spread it to all near Dirt, Grass, and Stone. \\n\\nMoss can be Sieved like Dirt but instead of getting Crops we'll get Saplings!]&f"]
	quest.6CCF2126B2BA72A6.title: "&2苔藓&7[Moss]&f"
	quest.70C2B568FA46337F.quest_desc: ["我们将需要大量的&7沙砾&f&r/&e沙子&f&r/尘土.所以让我们一次制造9倍的数量!\\n\\n将9个&8锤子&f&r合成一个&8&a压缩锤&f&r.这些可以&8锤击&f&r压缩方块,就像它们是普通方块一样.\\n\\n&7压缩圆石&f&r用&8锤子&f&r敲击会给出9个&7沙砾&f&r.\\n&7[We will need lots of Gravel/Sand/Dust. So let's make 9x more at a time! \\n\\nCombine 9 Hammers into a Compressed Hammer. These can Hammer Compressed Blocks as if they were normal Blocks. \\n\\nCompressed Cobble will give 9 Gravel with the Hammer.]&f"]
	quest.70C2B568FA46337F.title: "粉碎压缩方块&7[Crushing Compressed Blocks]&f"
	quest.79D6F21C1E1D1749.quest_desc: ["所有失败的&b&l空岛&f&r世界的创伤……&5黑曜石&f&r.\\n\\n正如许多&b&l空岛&f&r玩家所学到的,当&9水&f&r接触到一个&c熔岩源&f&r方块时,就会形成&5黑曜石&f&r.\\n\\n我们可以用&6&l木桶&f&r以更和平的方式做到这一点!\\n&7[The trauma of all failed lSkyblock Worlds... the Obsidian. \\n\\nAs many lSkyblock Players have learned, when Water touches a Lava Source Block it will make Obsidian. \\n\\nWe can do this in a more peaceful way by using lBarrels!]&f"]
	quest.79D6F21C1E1D1749.title: "&5黑曜石&7[Obsidian]&f"
	quest.7ADFD864139BF2F2.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到&b&l天空&f&r!\\n\\n你可能会注意到缺少……嗯,几乎一切!\\n\\n如果你有地面太多的问题(正常的&2世界&f&r,不是&b空岛&f&r),那么查看&9Discord&f&r中的FAQ来获得答案.\\n\\n使用命令”/skyblock gui\\n&7[Welcome to the lSky! \\n\\nYou might notice the lack of... well pretty much everything! \\n\\nIn case you have a problem of too much ground (normal World, not Skyblock) then check out the FAQ in the Discord to get your answer. \\n\\nUse the command \"/skyblock gui\" this will allow you to make a Team to start an Island! Select the type as well as the Name to get started. The rest of the configs are for Multiplayer.]&f"]
	quest.7ADFD864139BF2F2.quest_subtitle: "欢迎来到All The Mods 10:&a向天空进发&f!现在是两位数了.&7[Welcome to All The Mods 10: To the Sky! Now in double digits.]&f"
	quest.7ADFD864139BF2F2.title: "开始起步&7[Starting Out]&f"
	quest.7B08D4FC6F1B0005.quest_desc: ["放一些&9水&f&r到一个&6&l木桶&f&r里,然后把一个尘土方块扔进去得到&7黏土&f&r!\\n\\n你需要&a右击&f&6&l木桶&f&r来取出&7黏土&f&r.\\n\\n我们需要&7黏土&f&r来做一些东西,比如&c&a火焰砖&f&r和&3&a瓷土&f&r.\\n&7[Put some Water into a lBarrel then Toss a Dust Block into it to get Clay! \\n\\nYou'll need to Right Click the lBarrel to take out the Clay. \\n\\nWe will need Clay for a few things like Fire Bricks and Porcelain Clay.]&f"]
	quest.7B08D4FC6F1B0005.title: "&7黏土&7[Clay]&f"
	quest.7CC729E68A89D962.quest_desc: ["我们可以在&6&l木桶&f&r里混合&9水&f&r和牛奶来得到&a&a粘液块&f&r!\\n\\n这怎么做到的？\\n\\n我不知道!\\n\\n而且我真的不想知道!\\n&7[We can combine Water and Milk in a lBarrel to get Slime Blocks! \\n\\nHow does that work? \\n\\nI don't know! \\n\\nAnd I really don't want to know!]&f"]
	quest.7CC729E68A89D962.quest_subtitle: "黏糊糊的&7[Oopy goopy]&f"
	quest.7CC729E68A89D962.title: "&a粘液&7[Slime]&f"
	task.2019707AE4DAC703.title: "{atm9.quest.start1.emergency}"
	quest.02B4BF3175AE8E93.quest_desc: ["&2&lMA&f&r全是关于&2种子&f&r的,而要获得那些&2种子&f&r,我们需要建立一个&e&a注魔祭坛吧&f&r.\\n\\n放置&e&a注魔祭坛吧&f&r,并在其周围放置8个&e&a灌注基座&f&r.会有高亮显示来帮助你了解放置位置.\\n\\n&a朝向&f配方,种子基底将放在&e祭坛&f&r上,而物品将放在&e基座&f&r上.\\n\\n一旦它们都准备好了,给&e祭坛&f&r一个&c&a红石信号&f&r,它就应该激活.然后,新的&2种子&f&r或物品将在&e祭坛&f&r中生成.\\n&7[lMA is all about Seeds, and to get those Seeds we need an Infusion Altar set up. \\n\\nPlace the Infusion Altar with the 8 Infusion Pedestals around it. There will be highlights to help you know where to place them. \\n\\nLooking at Recipes, the Seed Base will go on the Altar while the Items will be placed on the Pedestals. \\n\\nOnce they are all ready, give the Altar a Redstone Signal and it should activate. Then, the new Seed or Item will spawn in the Altar.]&f"]
	quest.02B4BF3175AE8E93.title: "&e&a注魔祭坛吧&f&r设置&7[Infusion Altar set up]&f"
	quest.04B68D8613E4A81F.quest_desc: ["&b&l&aME控制器&f&r是整个&b&lAE2&f&r中最重要的方块.&bME系统&f&r的核心.没有&b&l&aME控制器&f&r,&b&lAE2&f&r中就没有任何东西.\\n\\n现在我们如何制作它？\\n\\n首先也是最简单的,是&b&a陨石&f&r.只需烧炼&b&a陨石粉&f&r!\\n\\n接下来是&5&a福鲁伊克斯粉&f&r.查看之前的任务来制作它.\\n\\n最后是&c&a工程处理器&f&r.这是通过使用&5&l压印器&f&r结合&c&a红石粉&f&f、一个&b&a工程处理器&f电路&f和&8&a硅板&f&r制成的!\\n&7[The lME Controller is the most important Block in all of lAE2. The Heart of the ME System. There is nothing in lAE2 without the lME Controller. \\n\\nNow how do we make it? \\n\\nFirst and the simplest, is Sky Stone. Just Smelt Sky Stone Dust! \\n\\nNext is Fluix Dust. Check out the previous Quest in order to make it. \\n\\nLast is the Engineering Processor. This is made from using an lInscriber to combine Redstone Dust, an Engineering Processor Circuit, and Printed Silicon!]&f"]
	quest.04B68D8613E4A81F.title: "&5&l&aME控制器&f&7[lME Controller]&f"
	quest.07A439B838E4BE61.quest_desc: ["&4储罐&f&r是为我们的&c&l铸造厂&f&r添加液体而制造的.\\n\\n主要是燃料.\\n\\n主要是&c熔岩&f&r!\\n\\n还有其他方式为我们的&c&l铸造厂&f&r提供燃料,但我们暂时不用担心那个.\\n\\n我们还需要&6液体加热线圈&f&r来构成&c&l铸造厂&f&r的地板.\\n\\n这些将被我们的燃料加热,并会熔化&c&l铸造厂&f&r中的物品.\\n&7[Tanks are made for adding Liquids into our lFoundry. \\n\\nMostly Fuel. \\n\\nMostly Lava! \\n\\nThere are other ways of Fueling up our lFoundry but we won't worry about that right now. \\n\\nWe'll also need Liquid Heating Coils to make up the Floor of the lFoundry. \\n\\nThese will be warmed up by our Fuel and will melt our Items in the lFoundry.]&f"]
	quest.07A439B838E4BE61.title: "&c&l铸造厂&f&r的&4储罐&f&r和&6加热&7[lFoundry Tanks and Heating]&f"
	quest.07BEB974DF1E5AD3.quest_desc: ["工作原理和&a铁发电机&f完全一样……只是好得多!\\n&7[Works exactly like an Iron Generator... just much better! ]&f"]
	quest.07BEB974DF1E5AD3.title: "&c&a下界合金发电机&f&7[Netherite Generator]&f"
	quest.08B60C5548530D6C.quest_desc: ["&4增强型&a生长加速器&f&r工作原理和&5&a生长加速器&f&r完全一样……只是更快!\\n\\n让我们专注于如何合成它吧!\\n\\n&5&a福鲁伊克斯珍珠&f&f就是&5&a福鲁伊克斯水晶&f&f、&5&a福鲁伊克斯粉&f&f和一个&3&a末影珍珠&f&r.\\n\\n&a破坏核心&f是石英、&5&a福鲁伊克斯粉&f&r和一个&c&a逻辑处理器&f&r.\\n\\n&a加速卡&f是&b&lAE2&f&r中存在的升级.我们用高级卡制作它们.那些需要&c&a运算处理器&f&r.\\n&7[Boosted Growth Accelerator works exactly like a Growth Accelerator... just even faster! \\n\\nLet's focus on how to Craft it then! \\n\\nFluix Pearls are just Fluix Crystals, Fluix Dust, and an Ender Pearl. \\n\\nAnnihilation Core is Quartz, Fluix Dust, and a Logic Processor. \\n\\nAcceleration Cards are Upgrades present in lAE2. We make them with Advanced Cards. Those need Calculation Processors. ]&f"]
	quest.08B60C5548530D6C.title: "&4增强型&a生长加速器&f&7[Boosted Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.09BF4A7F1C3426D4.quest_desc: ["&6&l地质矿石&f&r是我们在&b&lATM10TTS&f&r中资源自动化的主要方式.\\n\\n它们的工作原理像&5&a紫水晶母岩&f&r或&b赛特斯石英母岩&f&r.如果有空间,晶体将从它们的任何一侧生长出来.\\n\\n唯一的区别是&6&l地质矿石&f&r可以被镐子拾取!即使没有&a精准采集&f!\\n\\n&a水晶&f可以从&6萌芽地质矿石&f&r上开采下来,然后可以烧炼得到我们的锭.\\n\\n任何能加速&5紫水晶&f&r生长速度的方块也会加速&6地质矿石&f&r.\\n&7[lGeOre are our main Automation for Resources with lATM10TTS. \\n\\nThey work like Budding Amethyst or Certus. Crystals will grow out of any side of them if there is room. \\n\\nThe only difference is that lGeOres can be picked up by Pickaxes! Even without Silk Touch! \\n\\nThe Crystals can be Mined off of the Budding GeOre and can then be Smelt to get our Ingot. \\n\\nAny Blocks that boost the speed of Amethyst will also speed up GeOres.]&f"]
	quest.09BF4A7F1C3426D4.title: "&6&l地质矿石&7[lGeOre]&f"
	quest.0BDD1938BA14B2BE.quest_desc: ["用我们的 &9&a发光水晶碎片&f&r、一些 &7石头&r 和 &8宝石融合板岩&r(这些只是 &8深板岩 &f和 &5宝石粉尘&r),我们可以合成一个 &b钻石升级模板&r!\\n是的,&5&l&d神化&f&r 为我们提供了从 &7石头 &f到 &b钻石&r 的升级模板.这些可以帮助我们在升级物品时保留 &5附魔 &f和 &6词缀&r.\\n\\n我们需要一个 &b钻石升级模板&r 来合成一个……\\n&7[With our Luminous Crystal Shard, some Stone, and Gem-Fused Slates (these are just Deepslate and Gem Dust) we can Craft a Diamond Upgrade Template! \\nYeah, lApotheosis gives us Upgrade Templates from Stone to Diamond. These can help us keep Enchants and Affixes on an Item while upgrading it. \\n\\nWe will need a Diamond Upgrade Template in order to Craft a...]&f"]
	quest.0BDD1938BA14B2BE.title: "&b钻石升级模板&7[Diamond Upgrade Template]&f"
	quest.0D05288932D4542A.quest_desc: [
		"最基本且便宜的 &2&a生长加速器&f&r.\\n\\n但首先,什么是 &2&a生长加速器&f&r？&2&a生长加速器&f&r 通过促进附近任何 &2作物&r 或水晶的生长来工作.\\n\\n如果小麦与已供能的 &2&a生长加速器&f&r 相邻,它会生长得更快.如果 &5&a紫水晶母岩&f&r 与已供能的 &2&a生长加速器&f&r 相邻,它会更快地生长 &5紫水晶&r.\\n\\n&a手摇式 &a生长加速器&f&r 不使用能量,而是使用体力劳动!通过曲柄!\\n\\n在上面放置一个 &a木质曲柄&f,用 &a右击&f 转动它,它就会工作.\\n&7[The most basic and cheap Growth Accelerator. \\n\\nBut first, what are Growth Accelerators? Growth Accelerators work by boosting any Crops or Crystals near them, in Growth. \\n\\nIf Wheat is adjacent to a Powered Growth Accelerator, it will Grow much faster. If a Budding Amethyst is adjacent to a Powered Growth Accelerator it will Grow Amethyst faster. \\n\\nThe Cranked Growth Accelerator doesn't use Energy, instead it uses manual labor! Via Cranks! \\n\\nPlace a Wooden Crank on it, turn it with Right Click, and it will work.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_geore.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0D05288932D4542A.title: "&a手摇式 &a生长加速器&f&7[Cranked Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.0FDD6BD1005EE958.quest_desc: ["&8&l&a通量锤&f&r 会自动 &8锤击&r 物品.它不会消耗耐久度,而是消耗能量!\\n\\n我们需要在机器后面(开放的那一侧,轮子会在输出侧的右侧)放置一个容器,以便自动输出.\\n\\n然后,一旦方块被放入,它会 &8锤击&r 它们,并将新方块送入容器.\\n\\n我们还可以在后面放置一个 &b&l筛子&r,自动将 &7沙砾&r 扔进 &b&l筛子&r!\\n&7[The lFlux Hammer will automatically Hammer Items. It won't use Durability but rather it will use Energy! \\n\\nWe will need an Inventory behind the Machine (the side that is open, the wheel will be on the Right side of the Output side) in order to Automatically Output. \\n\\nThen, once the Blocks are put in, it will Hammer them and send the new Blocks into the Inventory. \\n\\nWe can also place a lSieve behind it to automatically throw Gravel into the lSieve!]&f"]
	quest.0FDD6BD1005EE958.title: "&l&8&a通量锤&f&7[lFlux Hammer]&f"
	quest.10B804035EFF34F9.quest_desc: ["&0&a凋灵骷髅&f&r 会在 &c下界要塞&r 中生成.\\n\\n它们有 3 格高,20 点 &4生命值&r,手持 &7&a石剑&f&r.\\n\\n听起来不太可怕,对吧？嗯,它们还会给你 &0凋零效果&r,这类似于 &2中毒&r,但会造成更多 &a伤害&f 并会杀死你!\\n\\n它们有几率掉落其 &0头颅&r,我们需要它来召唤 &0&l&a凋灵&f&r.\\n&7[Wither Skeletons will Spawn in Nether Fortresses. \\n\\nThey are 3 Blocks tall, with 20 Hearts, and a Stone Sword. \\n\\nDoesn't sound too scary do they? Well they also give you the Wither Effect which is like Poison but does more Damage and will Kill you! \\n\\nThey can rarely Drop their Skulls which we'll need in order to summon lThe Wither.]&f"]
	quest.10B804035EFF34F9.title: "&8&a凋灵骷髅&f&7[Wither Skeletons]&f"
	quest.16905BC2C6158311.quest_desc: ["好了,现在我们有了 &a生物生成&f 以及战利品收集器,现在只需要杀死怪物!\\n\\n&a铁钉刺&f 的合成并不便宜(也不容易),但它们绝对能胜任这项工作!\\n\\n任何接触到 &a铁钉刺&f 顶部的怪物都会受到 &a伤害&f.如果怪物死亡,它们会掉落战利品和 &a经验值&r.\\n\\n如果物品需要怪物明确被玩家杀死才能掉落,&a铁钉刺&f 不会掉落某些物品.\\n&7[Okay, now that we have Mob Spawning, as well as Loot Collectors, now we just need to Kill Mobs! \\n\\nIron Spikes aren't that cheap (or easy) to Craft, but they will definitely do the job! \\n\\nAny Mob that touches the top of Iron Spikes will take Damage. If the Mob dies, they will Drop their Loot and XP. \\n\\nThe Iron Spikes won't Drop certain Items if, the Item needs the Mob to explicitly be Killed by the Player. ]&f"]
	quest.17B49742F34F23B0.quest_desc: ["不喜欢&a铁钉刺&f或&b&a怪物捣碎器&f&r？为什么不试试&l&4尖刺尖刺&r!\\n\\n它们为我们提供了6种不同等级的尖刺.\\n\\n&4尖刺&r越昂贵,造成的&a伤害&f越高.但是……它们每次击杀还会产生不同的效果.\\n\\n&6&a木制尖刺&f&r不会杀死生物.&7石制尖刺&r不会掉落物品或&b经验&r.铁制尖刺会掉落物品但没有&b经验&r,而&e金制尖刺&r则相反.&b钻石尖刺&r提供玩家击杀掉落,并且可以像剑一样被&5附魔&r!&c下界合金尖刺&r能做&b钻石尖刺&r能做的所有事,外加&a防爆强化大板&f,甚至能抵御&0&l&a凋灵&f&r.\\n&7[Don't like Iron Spikes or Mob Mashers? Why not give lSpiky Spikes a try! \\n\\nThese give us 6 different Tiers of Spikes. \\n\\nThe more expensive the Spike, the more Damage. But... they also do different Effects per Kill. \\n\\nWooden Spikes won't Kill. Stone won't Drop Items or XP. Iron Drops Items but no XP while Gold does the opposite. Diamond gives Player Kill Drops plus it can be Enchanted like a Sword! Netherite does everything Diamond can do, plus Blast Resistance, even against lThe Wither.]&f"]
	quest.17B49742F34F23B0.title: "&l&4尖刺尖刺&7[lSpiky Spikes]&f"
	quest.1843C79133DFB024.quest_desc: ["最强大、最高效的发电机——&a下界之星发电机&f.猜猜它用什么来产生能量!\\n&7[The most powerful and efficient Generator, the Netherstar Generator. Take a guess what it uses to make Energy!]&f"]
	quest.1A97DDE49DB49E9D.quest_desc: [
		"4桶&a&a流体经验&f&r、任意类型的1颗&2种子&r,以及&a掉落自&f僵尸、骷髅、蜘蛛和苦力怕的物品,将为我们合成&5&a诅咒GM鸡饲料&f&r.\\n\\n这团由微塑料、基因改造和麸质组成的恶心物质可以喂给鸡,以获得&d&a腐烂鸡蛋&f&r.&a鸡&f无法承受所有的基因改造,会爆炸.\\n\\n我们可以将&d&a腐烂鸡蛋&f&r放在泥土上,制造&5&a诅咒之土&f&r.它最多可以形成5x5范围的&5&a诅咒之土&f&r.\\n\\n&5恐怖泥土&r会在黑暗时生成&c&a敌对性生物&f&r.生成速率大约是普通情况的10倍.甚至包括一些你不常看到的生物!\\n&7[4 Buckets of Fluid XP, one Seed of any type, as well as Drops from Zombies, Skeletons, Spiders, and Creepers will give us GM Chicken Feed Cursed. \\n\\nThis disgusting mass of microplastics, genetic modifications, and Gluten can be Fed to a Chicken to get a Rotten Egg. The Chickens can not handle all the genetic modification and will procede to explode. \\n\\nWe can place the Rotten Egg on Dirt to make Dreadful Dirt. It can make up to a 5x5 of Dreadful Dirt. \\n\\nDreaful Dirt will Spawn Hostile Mobs when Dark. Just at like 10 times the Rate. Even including some you don't see often!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_dreadful.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1A97DDE49DB49E9D.quest_subtitle: "For &c&a敌对性生物&f&7[For Hostile Mobs]&f"
	quest.1A97DDE49DB49E9D.title: "&5&a诅咒之土&f&7[Dreadful Dirt]&f"
	quest.1C73E60FC70408D4.quest_desc: ["终于有一个独特的发电机了!烹饪是食物的艺术.这些发电机不消耗煤炭、熔岩甚至原木,它们消耗食物.任何具有食物点数的物品都可以用来产生能量,产生的能量量基于该食物所含的食物点数.牛排比胡萝卜提供更多能量.\\n&7[Finally a unique Generator! Culinary is the name for the art of Food. These Generators don't take Coal, Lava, or even logs, they take Food. Anything with Food Points can be used to make Energy, the amount it makes is based off the amount of Food Points the Food consists of. Steak will give more Energy than a Carrot.]&f"]
	quest.1DB607AA14FBF2F7.quest_desc: ["&b&a怪物捣碎器&f&r是一个完美的&a屠宰机&f!\\n\\n它需要一个&c&a红石信号&f&r才能工作.\\n\\n任何接触到&b&a怪物捣碎器&f&r的生物都会被撕成碎片,是的,它们会像被玩家杀死一样掉落物品.\\n\\n像&8风扇&r一样,&b&a怪物捣碎器&f&r也可以升级.\\n\\n这些升级可以增加&a伤害&f、抢夺附魔,甚至赋予&a火焰附加&f效果!\\n&7[The Mob Masher is a perfect Killing Machine! \\n\\nIt will need a Redstone Signal to work. \\n\\nAny Mob that touches the Mob Masher will be torn to shreds and yes, they will Drop Items as if they were Killed by a Player. \\n\\nLike Fans, Mob Mashers can be upgraded. \\n\\nThese can increase Damage, Looting, and even give Fire Aspect!]&f"]
	quest.1DB607AA14FBF2F7.title: "&b&a怪物捣碎器&f&7[Mob Masher]&f"
	quest.1E3BEB94E0EEF222.quest_desc: ["&9定向&a生长加速器&f&r使用与&4增强型&a生长加速器&f&r相同的配方,只需将&a破坏核心&f替换为&a成型核心&f.\\n\\n&a成型核心&f需要&b赛特斯水晶&f、&5&a福鲁伊克斯粉&f&f和&c&a逻辑处理器&f&r.\\n\\n&9定向&a生长加速器&f&r的工作原理与其他&2&a生长加速器&f&r不同,区别在于它们的生长方式.它不会从萌芽水晶所有可能的方向生长晶体,而只会朝一个设定的方向生长.\\n\\n我们可以使用一个名为&9方向调节器&r的物品来设置&9定向&a生长加速器&f&r的方向.只需用它&a右击&f&9&a生长加速器&f&r即可改变方向.\\n\\n这些&9&a生长加速器&f&r是最快的,最适合自动化农场!\\n&7[Directional Growth Accelerators use the same Recipe as Boosted Growth Accelerators just replace the Annihilation Core with a Formation Core. \\n\\nFormation Cores need Certus Crystal, Fluix Dust, and a Logic Processor. \\n\\nThe Directional Growth Accelerator works different from the other Growth Accelerators by how they grow. Instead of Growing Crystals in each Direction available from the Budding Crystal, it will only Grow in one set Direction. \\n\\nWe can set the Direction in the Directional Growth Accelerator with an Item called a Direction Modifier. Just Right Click the Growth Accelerator with it to change the Direction. \\n\\nThese Growth Accelerators are the fastest and best for Auto Farms!]&f"]
	quest.1E3BEB94E0EEF222.title: "&9定向&a生长加速器&f&7[Directional Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.21912CB57B687E30.quest_desc: ["将8个8倍发电机与一个&a下界合金齿轮&f结合,制造一个64倍发电机!\\n\\n那可是一整组发电机!在……一个……方块里!\\n&7[Combine 8 8x Generators with a Netherite Gear to make a 64x Generator! \\n\\nThat is a whole stack of Generators! In... one... Block!]&f"]
	quest.21912CB57B687E30.title: "1个发电机容纳一整组&7[A whole stack in 1 Generator]&f"
	quest.24677171BCD906C4.quest_desc: ["&d&l末地&r仍然与&2&l原版&r完全相同,包括&5&l&a末影龙&f&r.\\n&5&l&a末影龙&f&r拥有150颗&4心&r,并且会从&5&a黑曜石柱&f&r上的&d&a末影水晶&f&r处恢复&4生命值&r.\\n\\n她拥有几种攻击方式:火球会在击中处扩散&d龙息&r；在她栖息于巢穴上方时倾泻&d龙息&r；或者直接用身体冲撞你.\\n破坏&d水晶&r,然后用箭射击她,直到她栖息在巢穴上方,再用你的剑砍她!\\n\\n一旦被杀死,她会掉落她的&5龙鳞&r、大量&a经验&r,并且她会打开传送门,并在巢穴上方留下她的&5龙蛋&r.记得拿走它!\\n&7[lThe End is still the exact same as lVanilla, including the lEnder Dragon. \\nThe lEnder Dragon has 150 Hearts and will regain Health from the End Crystals on the Obsidian Pillars. \\n\\nShe has a few Attacks: Fireballs which will spread Dragon's Breath wherever they hit, pouring Dragon's Breath where she is perched above her nest, or just ramming into you with her body. \\nBreak the Crystals, then Shoot her with Arrows until she perches above her Nest, then slice her with your Swords! \\n\\nOnce Killed she will Drop her Scales, tons of XP, plus she will open the Portal and give her Egg above the Nest. Remember to grab it!]&f"]
	quest.24677171BCD906C4.title: "&5&l&a末影龙&f&7[lEnder Dragon]&f"
	quest.258531A2C52ED845.quest_desc: ["等你们拿到&6全模因锭粒&r的时候,新章节可能已经发布了.\\n\\n好吧,这大大低估了你们,我知道这不是真的.\\n\\n不过,我们很快就会为&6&l全模因&r制作一个章节!\\n&7[By the time you guys get the AllTheModium Nugget the new Chapter will be out already. \\n\\nOkay, that was underestimating you guys a lot and I know that isn't true. \\n\\nWe'll make a Chapter for lAllTheModium soon though!]&f"]
	quest.25FBF7A3BD8A96B2.quest_desc: ["&5福鲁伊克斯&r对于&b&lAE2&r来说是一种非常神秘且有用的材料.我们需要相当多的它!\\n\\n要制作它,我们需要一些&9水&r和其他物品:&c&a红石粉&f&f、石英和&b充能赛特斯水晶&r.\\n\\n将所有这些东西扔进&9水&r中,等待片刻,我们就会得到2个&5&a福鲁伊克斯水晶&f&r!\\n&7[Fluix is a very mysterious and useful Material for lAE2. We'll need quite a bit of it! \\n\\nTo make it we'll need some Water and other Items: Redstone Dust, Quartz, and Charged Certus Crystal. \\n\\nToss all these Items into the Water, leave it for a second, and we'll get 2 Fluix Crystals!]&f"]
	quest.25FBF7A3BD8A96B2.title: "&5&a福鲁伊克斯水晶&f&7[Fluix Crystal]&f"
	quest.2A8588D77B5C74CA.quest_desc: ["查看&a手摇式&a生长加速器&f&r以了解&2&a生长加速器&f&r的一般工作原理.\\n\\n这个现在更昂贵了,需要&5福鲁伊克斯&r和石英来建造.\\n\\n它不依赖手动劳动工作,而是需要能量.能量可以来自&bME系统&r或其自身的能源.\\n&7[Check out the Cranked Growth Accelerator to learn how Growth Accelerators work in general. \\n\\nThis one is more expensive now needing Fluix and Quartz to build. \\n\\nInstead of working off manual labor, this one will need Energy. Either from an ME System or its own Energy Source.]&f"]
	quest.2A8588D77B5C74CA.title: "&5&a生长加速器&f&7[Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.2C320EC6C73F8F0A.quest_desc: ["&c下界要塞&r未被改动.它们仍然拥有相同的战利品、结构和生成.\\n\\n实际上,它们通常有更多的生成,因为生物没有其他地方可以生成!\\n&7[The Nether Fortresses are untouched. They still have same Loot, Structure, and Spawns. \\n\\nActually, they usually have more Spawns since there's no where else Mobs can spawn!]&f"]
	quest.2C320EC6C73F8F0A.title: "&c下界要塞&7[Nether Fortress]&f"
	quest.306BF72C2D2E544A.quest_desc: ["用4个&8&a灵魂沙&f&r摆成T形,并在&8&a灵魂沙&f&r上放置3个&0&a凋灵骷髅&f&r,我们将召唤&0&l&a凋灵&f&r.\\n\\n小心,&0&l&a凋灵&f&r在准备好战斗时会爆炸!\\n\\n&0&l&a凋灵&f&r拥有300颗&4心&r并且可以飞行.它会向你发射&0&a凋灵骷髅头骨&f&r,这些头骨会爆炸并对任何被击中者施加&0凋零效果&r.\\n\\n任何被&0&l&a凋灵&f&r杀死的生物都会掉落&0&a凋零玫瑰&f&r.\\n\\n一旦生命值降至150颗&4心&r,&0&l&a凋灵&f&r会飞得更低,并且不再受到投射物的&a伤害&f,所以你需要使用你的&a近程武器&f.\\n\\n一旦被杀死,它会掉落一些物品,包括&a下界之星&f.\\n&7[By making a T out of 4 Soul Sand and placing 3 Wither Skeletons on top of the Soul Sand, we will summon lThe Wither. \\n\\nCareful, lThe Wither will Explode when ready to Fight! \\n\\nlThe Wither has 300 Hearts and can Fly. It will Shoot Wither Skulls at you which Explode and give the Wither Effect to any who are Hit. \\n\\nAny Mobs that are Killed by lThe Wither will Drop Wither Roses. \\n\\nOnce taken down to 150 Hearts, lThe Wither will Fly lower and won't take Damage from Projectiles so you'll need to use your Melee Weapons. \\n\\nOnce Killed, it will Drop a few Items including the Nether Star.]&f"]
	quest.306BF72C2D2E544A.title: "&l&8&a凋灵&f&7[lThe Wither]&f"
	quest.30BF71B8E28163BB.quest_desc: ["&8&a灵魂沙&f&r是通过&b筛&r……猜猜看什么得到的.它需要&b钻石&r或&c下界合金&r筛网.\\n\\n所有涉及死亡的&2&lMA&r &2种子&r都需要&8&a灵魂沙&f&r.\\n\\n抱歉语气突然转变,但我只是实话实说!\\n&7[Soulium Dust is made from Sieving... take a guess. It'll need either a Diamond or Netherite Mesh. \\n\\nSoulium Dust will be needed for all lMA Seeds that involve Death. \\n\\nSorry for that switch in tone, but I'm just being honest!]&f"]
	quest.30BF71B8E28163BB.title: "&8&a灵魂沙&f&7[Soulium Dust]&f"
	quest.35E666FB9EAFA39B.quest_desc: ["让我们来烤个蛋糕吧!一个&d&a末地蛋糕&f&r!\\n\\n2杯糖、1个完整的鸡蛋、3个&e&a粉碎末地石&f&r？还有3个&3末影之眼&r？\\n\\n我怀疑用这些原料做出来的蛋糕味道会好!但它会将你传送到&d&l末地&r!\\n\\n&d&l末地&r与&2&l原版&r完全一样.我建议带一个&8路标&r,这样你可以更轻松地在两地之间传送.\\n&7[Let's Bake a Cake! An End Cake! \\n\\n2 cups of Sugar, 1 whole Egg, 3 Crushed Endstone? And 3 Eyes of Ender? \\n\\nI doubt the Cake will taste good with those ingredients! But it will Teleport you to lThe End! \\n\\nlThe End is perfectly normal to lVanilla. I'd recommend taking a Waystone so you can Teleport between each much easier.]&f"]
	quest.35E666FB9EAFA39B.title: "前往&d&l末地&7[Getting to lThe End]&f"
	quest.36AE40E537B22E1B.quest_desc: ["&8基础电容&r仅仅是&c&lPowah&r中众多、众多、众多配方中的开始,这些配方将被重复很多次.\\n&7[Basic Capacitors are just the start of the many, many, many Recipes needed in lPowah that will be repeated many a times.]&f"]
	quest.36AE40E537B22E1B.title: "&c&l能源动力&r&7[lPowah]&f"
	quest.3824439740223998.quest_desc: ["&8通量粉&r、&5黑曜石&r和&a末影之眼&r.\\n&8&l&d通量网络&f&r所需的一切!\\n&7[Flux Dust, Obsidian, and Eyes of Ender. \\nEverything we will need for lFlux Networks!]&f"]
	quest.3824439740223998.title: "&8&l&d通量网络&f&7[lFlux Networks]&f"
	quest.38FAA74C68B2E14C.quest_desc: ["&a&lMob Grinding Utils&r对于&a怪物农场&f建设非常有帮助,尤其是在像&b&l空岛&r这样的有限世界中!\\n\\n为了开始使用它,我们需要一些&a&a流体经验&f&r.为此,我们需要一个&5&a吸收漏斗&f&r和一个&a&a奇异储罐&f&r.\\n\\n&5&a吸收漏斗&f&r会拾取其周围特定区域内掉落的任何物品和&a经验&r并储存起来.\\n\\n查看&5&a吸收漏斗&f&r的GUI,以更改收集区域的位置,或者更改它将&a经验&r或物品发送到哪里.比如发送到我们的……\\n\\n&a&a奇异储罐&f&r,它会以&a&a流体经验&f&r的形式储存&a经验&r.然后,我们只需用桶&a右击&f&a储罐&r即可收集&a&a流体经验&f&r!\\n&7[lMob Grinding Utils is very helpful for Mob Farming, especially in limited Worlds like lSkyblock! \\n\\nIn order to start with it we'll need some Fluid XP. For that we need an Absorption Hopper and a Singularity Tank. \\n\\nThe Absorption Hopper will pick up any Items and XP dropped in a certain area around it and store it. \\n\\nCheck out the Absorption Hopper's GUI in order to change where the collecting area is, or where it sends XP or Items to. Like sending it to our... \\n\\nSingularity Tank which will store XP in the form of Fluid XP. Then, we can just Right Click the Tank with a Bucket to collect the Fluid XP!]&f"]
	quest.38FAA74C68B2E14C.title: "获取&a&a流体经验&f&7[Getting Fluid XP]&f"
	quest.3D0FE8A0EA0E9177.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到&l第2章&r!\\n\\n你现在应该已经能够获取大部分最简单的材料了,现在我们可以开始探索其他模组和农场了.\\n\\n你忘了这是一个&6&lATM整合包&r吗？你会需要农场的!\\n&7[Welcome to lChapter 2! \\n\\nYou should now have access to most of the simplest Materials, now we can start venturing into other Mods and Farms. \\n\\nDid you forget it is an lATM Modpack? You'll need Farms!]&f"]
	quest.3D0FE8A0EA0E9177.title: "&l精彩部分&7[lThe Cool Parts]&f"
	quest.3D73B9D876DAF356.quest_desc: [
		"终于我们可以开始从&b筛&r中获得一些真正的材料了!\\n\\n使用&b钻石&r和&c下界合金&r筛网,我们获得最稀有物品的最佳几率,以及大量新物品.\\n\\n我们现在可以从&e末地石&r中获得&5&a龙尘&f&f和&3&a深暗之域&f&r物品.从&8&a灵魂沙&f&r中获得&8灵魂质&f.从&e沙子&r中获得&a铀&f.从&0黑石&r中获得&b伊斯内石&f.\\n\\n最后,从&e沙子&f和&0黑石&r中都能获得&6全模因锭粒&r!\\n&7[Finally we can start getting some real Materials from Sieving! \\n\\nWith Diamond and Netherite Meshes we get the best chances for the rarest Items as well as plenty of new Items. \\n\\nWe can now get Draconium Dust and Deep Dark Items from Endstone. Soulium from Soul Sand. Urananite from Sand. Isneium from Blackstone. \\n\\nAnd finally AllTheModium Nuggets from both Sand and Blackstone!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_mesh.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.3D73B9D876DAF356.title: "最好的筛网!&7[The best Meshes!]&f"
	quest.40DB6E3DE87F16EF.quest_desc: [
		"&d龙息&r是一种强大的(臭的)且神秘的物品.强大意味着我们可以用它来制造能量,而且是大量的能量!&5&a口臭发电机&f&r利用&d龙息&r产生能量!\\n&7[Dragon's Breath is a powerful, (stinky), and mysterious item. Powerful means we can make Energy from it, and lots of it! Halitosis Generator makes Energy from Dragon's Breath!]&f"
		""
		"(顺便说一下,你可以用&dXY工艺&f的提取器配合龙首来刷取&d龙息&r).\\n&7[(BTW you can farm Dragon's Breath with an Extractor from XyCraft with a Dragon's Head).]&f"
	]
	quest.40DB6E3DE87F16EF.title: "&5&a口臭发电机&f&7[Halitosis Generator]&f"
	quest.419F9D82FFA2A6C4.quest_desc: ["&8&a怪物风扇&f&r是有用且易于配置的机器,专为移动生物而设计.\\n\\n默认情况下,它们在收到&c&a红石信号&f&r时激活.激活时,它们会将任何物品和生物吹向&8风扇&r前方5格处.\\n\\n&8风扇&r还带有我们可以合成并通过&a右击&f&8风扇&r添加的升级.它们可以吹得更宽、更高、更远!\\n&7[Mob Fans are useful and easily configured Machines designed to move Mobs. \\n\\nBy default they activate when given a Redstone Signal. When activated they will Blow any Items and Mobs to 5 Blocks in front of the Fan. \\n\\nFans also come with upgrades that we can Craft and add in by Right Clicking the Fan. They can Blow wider, higher, and farther!]&f"]
	quest.419F9D82FFA2A6C4.title: "&8风扇&7[Fans]&f"
	quest.4788B2DC0228CA50.quest_desc: ["用10个&5黑曜石&r,我们可以合成&c&a下界传送门&f&r.\\n\\n用&c火&r点燃它以启动它.然后,走进去前往&c&l&a地狱&f&r.\\n\\n你可能会注意到……&c&l地狱&f&r里缺少&c&l下界&r.希望你没忘记你正在玩一个&b&l空岛整合包&r!\\n\\n你可以建造方块来寻找&c下界要塞&r,或者只是建造平台让生物生成.顺便说一下,&5&a诅咒之土&f&r在&c&l&a地狱&f&r中也有效!\\n&7[With 10 Obsidian we can Craft the Nether Portal. \\n\\nLight it on Fire in order to start it. Then, walk on through to lThe Nether. \\n\\nYou might notice a lack of... lNether within lThe Nether. Hope you didn't forget you're playing a lSkyblock Modpack! \\n\\nYou can Build out Blocks to find Nether Fortresses or even just platforms for Mobs to Spawn. Dreadful Dirt works in lThe Nether BTW!]&f"]
	quest.4788B2DC0228CA50.title: "&c&l&a地狱&f&7[lThe Nether]&f"
	quest.481E60311ED46731.quest_desc: ["将8个相同的发电机与一个&a钻石齿轮&f结合,我们可以将发电机压缩成一个8倍发电机!\\n\\n这些发电机将以8个发电机的相同速率和&a效率&f工作,但只占用1台机器!\\n&7[By combining 8 of the same Generator with a Diamond Gear, we can compress the Generator into a 8x Generator! \\n\\nThese will work at the same Rate and Efficiency of 8 Generators, just in 1 Machine! ]&f"]
	quest.481E60311ED46731.title: "8倍发电机!&7[8x the Generator!]&f"
	quest.48BA757A68C25883.quest_desc: ["这些特殊的 &6词缀物品&r,非常稀有且难以获得,比其他物品更好!\\n\\n除了 &6词缀物品&r,我们还会得到一个 &5&l&d神化&f&r 宝石.\\n\\n在坠落的铁砧下压碎它.\\n\\n这会给我们 &5宝石粉尘&r!\\n\\n&5宝石粉尘&r 将用于许多配方,包括回收台.\\n&7[These special Affixed Items, the very rare and difficult ones to get, the ones better than other Items! \\n\\nAs well as the Affixed Item we will get an lApotheosis Gem. \\n\\nCrush it under a Falling Anvil. \\n\\nThis will give us Gem Dust! \\n\\nGem Dust will be needed for many Recipes including the Salvaging Table. ]&f"]
	quest.48BA757A68C25883.title: "&5宝石粉尘&7[Gem Dust]&f"
	quest.4C7E0034F317E49D.quest_desc: ["&a下级精华&r 不是挖矿或 &b筛&r 出来的,而是怪物的掉落物.像几乎每个怪物都会掉落.\\n\\n你需要大量的它才能进入 &2&l神秘农业&r,所以杀死足够的怪物来制作 &a下级精华种子&r.\\n\\n这些可以种植来收获 &a下级精华&r.\\n&7[Inferium Essence isn't Mined or Sieved, but it is a Drop from Mobs. Like almost every Mob. \\n\\nYou'll need tons of it to get into lMA so Kill enough Mobs to make the Infernium Seeds. \\n\\nThese can be Planted to farm Inferium.]&f"]
	quest.4C7E0034F317E49D.title: "&a下级精华&7[Inferium Essence]&f"
	quest.4DF0B04764C17642.quest_desc: ["在 &9夜晚&r,非常罕见地,一种与众不同的 &c敌对生物&r 会伴随着雷鸣般的登场而生成.\\n\\n这些怪物是来自 &5&l&d神化&f&r 的 Boss!\\n\\n它们比其他怪物拥有更多的 &4生命值&r、效果和装备.当我们杀死它们时,它们会掉落一个 &6词缀物品&r.\\n\\n这些是我们对 &5&l&d神化&f&r 的入门介绍.按 CTRL 和 T 键打开 &l世界等级&r 菜单!\\n&7[Very rarely at Night a Hostile Mob unlike any other will spawn in with a Thunderous entrance. \\n\\nThese Mobs are Bosses from lApotheosis! \\n\\nThey have more Hearts, Effects, and Gear than other Mobs. When we Kill them they'll Drop an Affixed Item. \\n\\nThese are our introductions to lApotheosis. Press CTRL and T to open up the lWorld Tier Menu!]&f"]
	quest.4DF0B04764C17642.title: "&5&l&d神化&f&r 冒险&7[lApotheosis Adventure]&f"
	quest.51D71CA472F930D1.quest_desc: [
		"4桶&b&a流体经验&f&r、某种&2种子&r以及4种精选&2作物&r将为我们带来&2营养&a鸡饲料&f&r.\\n\\n这4种&2作物&r或其&2种子&r均通过&b筛&r泥土获得.\\n\\n&2营养&a鸡饲料&f&r可以喂给鸡,以获得一枚&e&a金鸡蛋&f&r!(代价是鸡的生命.)\\n\\n&e&a金鸡蛋&f&r可以放置在泥土上,最多能生成一个5x5区域的&2&a祈福之土&f&r.\\n\\n&2&a祈福之土&f&r生成&a&a被动型生物&f&r的频率远高于普通泥土.它甚至可能生成一些你很少见到的生物!\\n&7[4 Buckets of Fluid XP, some sort of Seed, and 4 select Crops will get us Nutritional Chicken Feed. \\n\\nThe 4 Crops or their Seeds are all obtained through Sieving Dirt. \\n\\nNutritional Chicken Feed can be Fed to a Chicken in order to get a Golden Egg! (At the cost of a Chicken's life.) \\n\\nThe Golden Egg can be Placed on Dirt and will make at most a 5x5 Area of Delightful Dirt. \\n\\nDelightful Dirt will Spawn Passive Mobs much more commonly than normal Dirt. It might even Spawn some you rarely see!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_delightful.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.51D71CA472F930D1.quest_subtitle: "For &a&a被动型生物&f&7[For Passive Mobs]&f"
	quest.51D71CA472F930D1.title: "&2&a祈福之土&f&7[Delightful Dirt]&f"
	quest.54369B8F151CAFAB.quest_desc: ["将&7黏土球&r与&e沙子&r结合,我们可以制作&c&a耐火黏土块&f&r.\\n\\n烧炼那个&c&a耐火黏土块&f&r以获得&c&a火焰砖&f&r!然后,将4块&c&a火焰砖&f&r组合,作为我们&c&l熔铸炉&r的开端.\\n\\n它会制作出&0黑色&a火焰砖&f&r,但你可以给它们染色,所以没问题!\\n&7[By combining Clay balls with Sand we can make Fire Clay. \\n\\nSmelt that Fire Clay to get Fire Bricks! Then, combine 4 Fire Bricks to make the start to our lFoundry. \\n\\nIt will make Black Fire Bricks but you can Dye them so it is okay!]&f"]
	quest.54369B8F151CAFAB.title: "制作&c&l熔铸炉&7[Making the lFoundry]&f"
	quest.5590E979DBE4E09B.quest_desc: ["&0&a绝缘覆层&f&r将是&c&lPowah&r所需的!\\n\\n有趣的是,它有两种配方.1:3个&0煤炭&r、2个&7黏土&r和1桶&c岩浆&r.2:2个&0煤炭&r、1个&7黏土&r和1个&c&a烈焰粉&f&r.\\n\\n使用&c岩浆&r的配方会产出24个&0&a绝缘覆层&f&r,而使用&c&a烈焰粉&f&r的配方产出16个.\\n\\n”哇,一个配方给这么多!”其实并不多!这个模组将需要数十亿个&0&a绝缘覆层&f&r.\\n\\n你会祈祷配方能产出24,000个!\\n&7[Dielectric Paste will be needed for lPowah! \\n\\nIt has 2 Recipes funny enough. 1: 3 Coal, 2 Clay, and a Bucket of Lava. 2: 2 Coal, 1 Clay, and 1 Blaze Powder. \\n\\nThe Lava one will give 24 Dielectric Paste while the Blaze Powder gives 16. \\n\\n\"Wow that seems like a lot for 1 Recipe!\" IT IS NOT! This Mod will need BILLIONS of Dielectric Paste. \\n\\nYou're going to pray that the Recipe gave 24,000!]&f"]
	quest.5590E979DBE4E09B.title: "&8&a绝缘覆层&f&7[Dielectric Paste]&f"
	quest.56370EFB8C300AE5.quest_desc: ["&e&a粉碎末地石&f&r的奖励物品相当简单.\\n\\n&3&a末影珍珠&f&f、&a末影之眼&f、&d&a紫颂果果实&f&f和&d花&r.\\n\\n不过,一旦我们开始使用&b钻石&f和&c下界合金&r筛网,就能得到一些好东西!\\n\\n此外,你还可以制作美味的魔法&d蛋糕&r!\\n&7[Crushed Endstone gives pretty simple Items as rewards. \\n\\nEnder Pearls, Eyes of Ender, Chorus Fruits and Flowers. \\n\\nOnce we start using Diamond and Netherite Meshes though, then we get some good stuff! \\n\\nPlus you can make a yummy magical Cake!]&f"]
	quest.56370EFB8C300AE5.title: "&e&a粉碎末地石&f&7[Crushed Endstone]&f"
	quest.5893A5D20E77D98B.quest_desc: ["在&b&lATM10TTS&r中,我们能找到的唯一刷怪笼位于&c下界要塞&r.\\n\\n我们拥有&5&l&d神化&f&r,所以带上你的&a精准采集&f去偷走那些刷怪笼吧!\\n\\n然后,你就可以随心所欲地编辑它了.\\n&7[The only Spawners we can find in lATM10TTS is in Nether Fortresses. \\n\\nWe got lApotheosis so take your Silk Touch and steal those Spawners! \\n\\nThen, you can Edit it as much as you want.]&f"]
	quest.5A71A1F11FB74BDA.quest_desc: [
		"&8&d通量网络&f&r的核心是&8通量&r!&8通量&r是通过用&5黑曜石&r将&c红石&r在&8基岩&f上压碎制成的!\\n\\n我们没有&8基岩&r,但我们有&5&a一重压缩黑曜石&f&r.一重压缩的已经足够接近了!\\n\\n放置&5一重压缩黑曜石&r,在其上方一格处放置普通&5黑曜石&r,中间留出一格空隙.将&c&a红石粉&f&r扔到它们之间,然后&a左击&f顶部的&5黑曜石&r来压碎它.\\n\\n这将给我们&8通量粉&r!\\n&7[Flux Networks is all about Flux! Flux is made from Crushing Redstone against Bedrock with Obsidian! \\n\\nWe don't have Bedrock, but we do have Compressed Obsidian. Which 1X is close enough! \\n\\nPlace 1x Obsidian, with normal Obsidian above it with a 1 Block Gap. Throw the Redstone Dust between them and Left Click the top Obsidian to Crush it. \\n\\nThis will give us Flux Dust!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_flux1.png width:50 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_flux2.png width:50 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5A71A1F11FB74BDA.title: "压碎获取&8通量粉&7[Crushing for Flux Dust]&f"
	quest.5AAE3E43A8A545C4.quest_desc: ["&b&l&a通量筛子&f&r和&8&l锤子&r都可以进行升级!\\n\\n这些升级将提高它们的工作速度和处理的物品数量.\\n每种升级最多可以叠加3个,数量越多,效果越好.\\n&7[Both the lFlux Sieve and lHammer can have Upgrades! \\n\\nThese will increase how quickly they work and how many Items they process. \\nYou can stack up to 3 of each, the more you have the better they are.]&f"]
	quest.5AAE3E43A8A545C4.title: "通量升级&7[Flux Upgrades]&f"
	quest.5AE7A856B4CEB97A.quest_desc: ["&7&a实体传送带&f&r是我最喜欢的移动生物的工具之一.\\n\\n生物可以在&7传送带&r顶部生成,除非它们需要特定的方块才能生成.\\n\\n&7&a实体传送带&f&r会按照它们放置的方向移动生物.\\n\\n我们无法让它们移动得更快,只有&8风扇&r可以升级.\\n&7[Entity Conveyors are some of my favorites to move Mobs. \\n\\nMobs can Spawn on top of Conveyors, unless they need a specific Block to Spawn on. \\n\\nEntity Conveyors will move Mobs in the direction they are Placed in. \\n\\nWe can't make them go faster, only Fans can be upgraded.]&f"]
	quest.5AE7A856B4CEB97A.title: "&7&a实体传送带&f&7[Entity Conveyors]&f"
	quest.5D5DE276D2746B46.quest_desc: ["有了我们的&c&a远古残骸&f&r,我们可以烧炼它来获得&c&a下界合金碎片&f&r.\\n\\n(顺便说一句,仅用9个&c碎片&r我们就可以制作一个&c下界合金地质矿石&r!)\\n\\n现在我们可以制作&c&a下界合金锭堆&f&r了!\\n\\n不幸的是,几乎所有的东西都需要一个&c下界合金升级模板&r……\\n&7[With our Ancient Debris, we can Smelt it to get Netherite Scraps. \\n\\n(Btw, with only 9 Scraps we can make a Netherite GeOre!) \\n\\nNow we can make Netherite Ingots! \\n\\nUnfortunately almost everything will need a Netherite Upgrade Template as well...]&f"]
	quest.5D5DE276D2746B46.title: "&c&a下界合金锭&f&7[Netherite Ingot]&f"
	quest.603816519B62044F.quest_desc: ["&5&l&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f&r如今是&b&lTo The Sky&r的常客了.我不怪他们,这是一个有趣且超强的模组!\\n\\n&5&l&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f&r的核心是&a聚合装置&f和模块.这两者都需要&5&a龙尘&f&r.\\n\\n这里会有一个&5&l&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f&r的任务线……如果它不再那么难的话!\\n&7[lDraconic Evolution is a usual for lTo The Sky now. I don't blame them, it is a fun and overpowered Mod! \\n\\nlDraconic Evolution is all about Fusion Crafting and Modules. Both of these will need Draconium Dust. \\n\\nThere will be a Questline for lDraconic Evolution here... if it stops being difficult!]&f"]
	quest.603816519B62044F.title: "&5&l&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f&7[lDraconic Evolution]&f"
	quest.615D8F153DBF3C9C.quest_desc: ["&8钢&r将被用于许多模组,包括&5&l&d通用机械&f&r!\\n\\n要获得它,我们需要建造一个&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r.同时,它还需要能量、&0煤炭&r和&7铁&r.\\n\\n给&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r提供一些能量,然后将&0煤炭&f放入&e黄色方格&f,&7铁&f放入&4红色方格&r.\\n&7[Steel will be used for quite a lot of Mods, including lMekanism! \\n\\nTo get it, we'll need to Build a lMetallurgic Infuser. As well, it will need Energy, Coal, and Iron. \\n\\nFeed the lMetallurgic Infuser some Energy, then place the Coal in the Yellow Square and Iron in the Red Square.]&f"]
	quest.615D8F153DBF3C9C.title: "制作&8钢&7[Making Steel]&f"
	quest.61F265D9A5713A4D.quest_desc: ["&6&lGenerator Galore&r变化相当大!\\n\\n它们的功能都一样,消耗物品产生能量,但它们的类型和配方已经改变.\\n\\n我们现在不需要&6铜&f、&e金&f和&b钻石&r发电机了,现在只有铁、&c下界合金&r和独特的发电机.\\n除了&4&a岩浆发电机&f&r,所有发电机都从&a铁发电机&f开始!\\n&7[lGenerator Galore has changed quite a bit! \\n\\nThey function all the same, use Item get Energy, but their types and Recipes have changed. \\n\\nWe don't need Copper, Gold, and Diamond Generators now we just have Iron, Netherite, and unique Generators. \\nAll but the Magmatic Generator start with the Iron Generator!]&f"]
	quest.61F265D9A5713A4D.quest_subtitle: "&a铁发电机&f&7[Iron Generator]&f"
	quest.61F265D9A5713A4D.title: "&6&l发电机盛宴&r&7[lGenerator Galore]&f"
	quest.64B72C477EA7E6CA.quest_desc: ["&b引流器&r是我们用来提取材料的工具.是的,不幸的是,对于我们的手或桶来说,它太烫了.\\n\\n将&c&l熔铸炉&r的&7龙头&r连接到&b引流器&r,&a右击&f龙头即可排出材料.\\n\\n查看&b引流器&r时,你还可以看到&c&l熔铸炉&r中液体的数量!\\n&7[Drains are what we'll use to extract our the Materials. Yes, it will unfortunately be too hot for our Hands or Buckets. \\n\\nConnect the lFoundry Tap to the Drain, to drain out the Materials when Right Clicking the Tap. \\n\\nYou can also view the amounts of Liquids in the lFoundry when viewing the Drain!]&f"]
	quest.64B72C477EA7E6CA.title: "&c&l熔铸炉&r的&b引流器&f和&7龙头&7[lFoundry Drains and Taps]&f"
	quest.65CE3B5FCD759ABC.quest_desc: ["在&b空岛生存&f中,我们需要长时间进行&b筛&f和&8锤&r,不幸的是,并非每个农场都能替代它.\\n\\n好吧,至少有了&b&lEx Machinis&r,我们可以以能量为代价,完全自动化&b筛&r和&8锤&r!\\n&7[We'll need to keep Sieving and Hammering for a long time with Skyblock, unfortunately not every Farm will replace it. \\n\\nWell, atleast with lEx Machinis we can fully Automate Sieving and Hammering with the Cost of Energy!]&f"]
	quest.65CE3B5FCD759ABC.title: "&b空岛生存&r自动化&7[Skyblock Automation]&f"
	quest.6712DF74C4972D56.quest_desc: ["&c下界合金升级模板&r!\\n\\n我们的&c&l下界&r有点缺乏堡垒遗迹,所以我们必须合成它们.\\n\\n我的意思是,你可以使用&b&l&d神秘学&f&r来获得它们……但那比&5&l&d神化&f&r的方式难多了!\\n&7[Netherite Upgrade Templates! \\n\\nOur lNether is a little devoid of Bastions so instead we have to Craft them. \\n\\nI mean you can use lOccultism to get them... but that's much harder than lApotheosis way!]&f"]
	quest.6712DF74C4972D56.title: "&c下界合金升级模板&7[Netherite Upgrade Template]&f"
	quest.68972BA647FDCF8F.quest_desc: ["如果你知道&l&6&d资源蜜蜂&f&r,你应该知道LobsterJonn.他制作了&l&6&d资源蜜蜂&f&r和&l&6Generator's Galore&r(以及许多其他模组).&6&a蜂蜜发电机&f&r是连接这两个模组的好方法!&6&a蜂蜜发电机&f&r使用&6液态蜂蜜&r来产生能量.\\n&7[If you know lProductive Bees you should know LobsterJonn. He made lProductive Bees and lGenerator's Galore (along with many others). The Honey Generator is a good way of connecting both these mods! Honey Generator uses Liquid Honey to make Energy. ]&f"]
	quest.68972BA647FDCF8F.title: "&6&a蜂蜜发电机&f&7[Honey Generator]&f"
	quest.69201157ECFBB426.quest_desc: ["我总是讨厌当我有一个&5末影人&r农场来获取经验或&d神化&f宝石时,最终却得到所有这些&3&a末影珍珠&f&r(嘿嘿,最终,&3末影珍珠&r).现在你可以用那些&3&a末影珍珠&f&r通过&3&a末影发电机&f&r来产生能量.你甚至可以用&a末影之眼&r来产生更多能量!\\n&7[I always hate when I have an Endermen Farm for either XP or Apotheosis Gems but end up with all these Ender Pearls (hehe end up, ender pearls). Now you can use those Ender Pearls for Energy with the Ender Generator. You can even make Eyes of Ender for even more Energy!]&f"]
	quest.69201157ECFBB426.title: "&3&a末影发电机&f&7[Ender Generator]&f"
	quest.6A1145678E80FB8E.quest_desc: ["有那么多没用的&5附魔&r,为什么不从中获取一些能量呢!&b&a附魔发电机&f&r使用&5&a附魔书&f&r来产生能量.&5&a附魔书&f&r的等级和稀有度会影响你从中获得的能量数量.\\n&7[There's so many useless Enchantments out there, why not get some Energy out of them! The Enchantment Generator uses Enchanted Books to make Energy. The Level and Rarity of Enchanted Books changes the amount of Energy you get from them.]&f"]
	quest.6A1145678E80FB8E.title: "&b&a附魔发电机&f&7[Enchantment Generator]&f"
	quest.6AAE1DA641CBD6A6.quest_desc: ["我们可以&b筛&r沙砾来获得&b&a陨石粉&f&r.\\n\\n这将是我们制作压印模板所需要的.\\n\\n我们也可以在其他配方中使用它,或者烧炼它来获得&b&a陨石&f&r.\\n&7[We can Sieve Dust in order to get Sky Stone Dust. \\n\\nThis will be needed in order to make our Presses. \\n\\nWe can also use it in other Recipes or Smelt it to get Sky Stone.]&f"]
	quest.6AAE1DA641CBD6A6.title: "&b&a陨石&f&7[Sky Stone]&f"
	quest.6B4AD4927B665338.quest_desc: ["&3&a回响碎片&f&r以在&6远古城市&r中找到的物品而闻名……但我们没有.或者作为&3&l监守者&r的&a掉落物&f……我们目前还无法生成……\\n\\n好吧,我们总是可以&b筛&r&e末地石&r,有极小的几率获得它们!\\n\\n&3&a回响碎片&f&r是许多昂贵且强大的合成所必需的.包括……\\n&7[Echo Shards are known for being Items found in the Ancient Cities... which we don't have. Or as Drops from the lWarden... which we can't Spawn in yet... \\n\\nWell we can always Sieve Endstone for a rare chance at them! \\n\\nEcho Shards are needed for lots of expensive and powerful Crafts. Including the...]&f"]
	quest.6B4AD4927B665338.title: "&3&a深暗之域&f&r物品&7[Deep Dark Items]&f"
	quest.6C3E384FBDE74A8E.quest_desc: ["&6&l机械动力&r在这里会被大量使用.\\n我们获得了它的1.21新版本以及自动&5附魔&r!希望你不会对它感到厌倦!\\n\\n你需要大量的&7安山岩&r,你应该庆幸它现在可以自动化了.\\n&7[lCreate is going to be used here a lot. \\nWe got its new 1.21 Update as well as the automatic Enchanting! Hope you don't get sick of it! \\n\\nYou'll need a ton of Andesite for it, you should be glad it's automated now.]&f"]
	quest.6C3E384FBDE74A8E.title: "&6&l机械动力&7[lCreate]&f"
	quest.6C8DB9997F9D5B62.quest_desc: ["&a控制器&r是&c&l熔铸炉&r的核心.\\n\\n每个&c&l熔铸炉&r至少需要1个控制器才能制作.\\n\\n我们可以使用&c&l熔铸炉&r来查看其GUI.在这里我们可以看到&c&l熔铸炉&r内液体的数量.\\n\\n我们还可以用它来放入和取出&c&l熔铸炉&r中的物品.\\n&7[The Controller is the heart of the lFoundry. \\n\\nEach lFoundry will need atleast 1, to be made. \\n\\nWe can use the lFoundry to view the GUI of the lFoundry. Here we can see the amounts of Liquids within the lFoundry. \\n\\nWe can also use it to put and take Items in and out of the lFoundry.]&f"]
	quest.6C8DB9997F9D5B62.title: "&c&l熔铸炉&r的&a控制器&7[lFoundry Controller]&f"
	quest.6D05CA4C501AAC9C.quest_desc: ["&a挽危&f工作台将为我们提供宝石的&5宝石粉&r以及物品的稀有度碎片!\\n\\n每个&6词缀物品&r都有一个稀有度:&7普通&f、&a罕见&f、&9稀有&f、&5史诗&f和&6传说&r.这些会给我们一个匹配的稀有度碎片.\\n\\n我们需要&9发光&a水晶碎片&f&r,它来自拆解&9稀有词缀物品&r!\\n&7[The Salvaging Table will give us Gem Dust for Gems as well as Rarity Shards from Items! \\n\\nEach Affixed Item has a Rarity: Common, Uncommon, Rare, Epic, and Legendary. These will give us a matching Rarity Shard. \\n\\nWe need Lumious Crystal Shards, which come from Salvaging Rare Affixed Items!]&f"]
	quest.6D9F5C88564B009F.quest_desc: ["使用廉价的筛网&0筛&r碎黑石只会给出少数与&c&l下界&r或&0黑色&r相关的物品.比如&c岩浆&f和&0&a黑色染料&f&r!\\n\\n但它们也能给出&c&a远古残骸&f&r!\\n\\n筛网等级越高,获得它的几率就越大.\\n\\n这仍然是一个非常低的几率,只是比以前稍微高一点!\\n&7[Crushed Blackstone with cheap Meshes will only give a few lNether or Black related Items. Like Magma and Black Dye! \\n\\nBut they can also give Ancient Debris! \\n\\nThe higher the Mesh, the better the Chance to get it. \\n\\nIt is still a very low Chance, just slightly higher than before!]&f"]
	quest.6D9F5C88564B009F.title: "&8碎黑石&7[Crushed Blackstone]&f"
	quest.6DB2D7D50AE1DA18.quest_desc: ["&3幽匿核心&r.它可以用于一个非自然的&3&a幽匿尖啸体&f&r,使其能够生成&3&l&a监守者&f&r.\\n\\n&3幽匿核心&r由4个&3&a回响碎片&f&r和1个&3&a末影珍珠&f&r制成.\\n\\n&3&a幽匿尖啸体&f&r可以通过&b筛&r获得.&3&a幽匿尖啸体&f&r也会像正常一样工作,它们仍然会因声音而蔓延!\\n&7[Sculk Core. Which can be used on a unnatural Sculk Shrieker to allow them to Spawn lThe Warden. \\n\\nSculk Cores are made from 4 Echo Shards and 1 Ender Pearl. \\n\\nThe Sculk Shriekers can be obtained from Sieving. Sculk Shriekers will work like normal as well, they still spread from Sound!]&f"]
	quest.6DB2D7D50AE1DA18.title: "生成&3&l&a监守者&f&7[Spawning lThe Warden]&f"
	quest.6DC80D4BB5DE54D5.quest_desc: ["&b赛特斯石英水晶&r过去生长在陨石中找到的&b赛特斯石英芽&r里!但我想陨石太多了,地面无法承受,所以消失了.\\n\\n取而代之的是,我们现在可以从&b筛&r&e沙子&r中获得它们.\\n\\n我们还可以从&b筛&r&e沙子&r中获得&b充能赛特斯石英水晶&r,或者使用&c&l充能器&r!\\n\\n&c&l充能器&r是一种可以使用曲柄或能量来给物品充能的机器.\\n\\n我们还可以将一个&b充能赛特斯石英水晶&r与&b赛特斯石英粉&r一起扔进&9水&r中,以制作2个&b赛特斯石英水晶&r.&b赛特斯石英粉&r通过&b筛&r沙砾获得!\\n&7[Certus Crystals used to grow in Budding Certus Crystals found within Meteorites! But I guess there were so many Meteorites that the ground couldn't handle it and disappeared. \\n\\nInstead we can now get them from Sieving Sand. \\n\\nWe can also get Charged Certus Crystals from Sieving Sand, or use the lCharger! \\n\\nThe lCharger is a Machine that can either use a Crank or Energy to Charge Items. \\n\\nWe can also throw a Charged Certus Crystal with Certus Dust in Water to make 2 Certus Crystals. Certus Dust is obtained through Sieving Dust!]&f"]
	quest.6DC80D4BB5DE54D5.title: "&b赛特斯石英水晶&r 与充能&7[Certus Crystals and Charging]&f"
	quest.6FDB420BD5FF1E6B.quest_desc: [
		"别再捡&7鹅卵石&r了,捡这些吧!\\n\\n没错,你没听错!我们可以用&7&l&a圆石制造机&f&r来自动化生产&7安山岩&r.\\n\\n像平常一样建造它,但在它下面放一个&7安山岩方块&r,它就会制造&7安山岩&r而不是&7圆石&r!\\n&7[Quit picking up Pebbles, pick up these instead! \\n\\nYeah you heard me right! We can automate Andesite with the lCobble Generator. \\n\\nBuild it like normal but place an Andesite Block beneath it and it will make Andesite instead of Cobble!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_gen.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6FDB420BD5FF1E6B.title: "自动化&7安山岩&7[Automating Andesite]&f"
	quest.716B9E90D1A0F120.quest_desc: [
		"&l&bAE2&r很复杂.不然你以为我为什么躲了它这么久？但我们会试着让它……不那么复杂？\\n\\n使用我们的&5&l压印器&r,我们可以将某些物品与&a铁板&f结合来制作&7压印模板&r.\\n\\n我们需要全部4种&7模板&r,不过这没关系,它们还算容易获得.\\n\\n我们需要这些来制作&c电路&r,翻到下一页了解它们!\\n&7[lAE2 is complicated. Why do you think I avoided it for so long? But we'll try and make it... less complicated? \\n\\nUsing our lInscriber we can combine certain Items with Iron Plates to make Inscriber Presses. \\n\\nWe will need all 4 of these Presses but that is okay, they're decently easy to get. \\n\\nWe'll need these in order to make Circuits, flip the page to read about those!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&5&l压印器&r不仅能制作&7模板&r,还能制作&c电路&r……使用那些&7模板&r.\\n\\n每种&7模板&r都可以与一种材料结合,制成特殊的&c电路&r.\\n\\n这些&c电路&r需要在&5&l压印器&r中相互结合,制成完整的&c电路&r.这些是制造我们机器的最终产品.\\n\\n不过,我不保证这一点……&b&lAE2&r很复杂.\\n&7[lInscribers don't just make Presses, they also make Circuits... using those Presses. \\n\\nEach Press can be combined with a Material to make a special Circuit. \\n\\nThese Circuits will need to be combined with each other in an lInscriber to make completed Circuits. These are the final products to create our Machines. \\n\\nI don't promise that though... lAE2 is complicated.]&f"
	]
	quest.716B9E90D1A0F120.title: "&7压印模板&f和&c电路&7[Inscriber Presses and Circuits]&f"
	quest.725E8046DA60CFA3.quest_desc: ["&b&a活化水晶碎片&f&r可以通过用&a铁网&f或更好的筛子筛&8&a灵魂沙&f&r获得.\\n\\n它们用于制作&b繁荣种子&r,而繁荣种子可以制作几乎所有的&2&lMA&r &2种子&r!\\n\\n所以,它们有点重要.\\n\\n一定要开始囤积它们!\\n&7[Prosperity Shards are gained from Sieving Soul Sand with an Iron Mesh or better. \\n\\nThey are needed to make Prosperity Seeds, which make almost every single lMA Seed! \\n\\nSo, they are kinda important. \\n\\nDefinitely start stocking up on them!]&f"]
	quest.725E8046DA60CFA3.title: "&b&a活化水晶碎片&f&7[Prosperity Shards]&f"
	quest.7297391D026EE9A6.quest_desc: ["想要一些刺激又新颖的产能方式吗？用&d药水&r怎么样!这就是&d&a药水发电机&f&r的作用,它会根据药水的强度和持续时间,将你的&d药水&r转化为能量.\\n&7[Want something exciting and new to make Energy? What about using Potions for it! That's what the Potion Generator does, it will take your Potions and make Energy out of it depending on its strength and duration.]&f"]
	quest.7297391D026EE9A6.title: "&d&a药水发电机&f&7[Potion Generator]&f"
	quest.72DD9E63B22C08E3.quest_desc: ["使用我们改造过的&3&a幽匿尖啸体&f&r,我们可以将其激活&a可用 3 次&f来生成&3&l&a看守兽&f&r.\\n&3&l&a看守兽&f&r在&b&l天空&r中同样强大,拥有 500 &4颗心&r的生命值和大量的&a伤害&f!并且它们还拥有&b音波射线&r.\\n\\n幸运的是,它们依然和原来一样瞎,即使是在数百格高的空中!利用这一点来击败它们.保持距离,保持安静.\\n\\n你最好的策略是到达&3&l&a看守兽&f&r上方 23 格的位置,然后用箭矢狂射它.&3&l&a看守兽&f&r的&b音波射线&r射程无法超过 23 格.\\n\\n它的掉落物仍然是&5&l&d神化&f&r所需的!\\n&7[With our modified Sculk Shrieker we can set it off 3 times to Spawn lThe Warden. \\nlThe Warden is still just as powerful in the lSky with 500 Hearts and a ton of Damage! As well as having their Sonic Beam. \\n\\nThankfully they are still just as Blind, even hundreds of Blocks up! Use this to your advantage to take them down. Keep your distance, and stay quiet. \\n\\nYour best bet would be to get 23 Blocks above lThe Warden and to spam Arrows at it. lThe Warden can't shoot its Sonic Beam over 23 Blocks. \\n\\nIts Drops are still needed for lApotheosis!]&f"]
	quest.72DD9E63B22C08E3.title: "&3&l&a看守兽&f&7[lThe Warden]&f"
	quest.7455D154FD1B4716.quest_desc: ["&b&l&a通量筛子&f&r需要满足一系列不同的条件才能工作.\\n\\n第一,是能量.这个你可以自己想办法解决.\\n\\n第二,是它下方需要一个容器.它可以从任何侧面输入,但需要下方有一个容器来输出.\\n\\n第三,是筛网.筛网的类型将决定从&b筛矿&r中获得什么物品.\\n\\n一旦你准备好所有东西,将方块自动化输入到&b&l&a通量筛子&f&r中,它就会把资源放入下方的容器里!\\n&7[The lFlux Sieve needs a bunch of different requirements to work. \\n\\nFirst, is Energy. You can worry about that on your own. \\n\\nSecond, is an Inventory beneath it. It can Input any Side but it needs an Inventory beneath it to Output. \\n\\nThird, is a Mesh. The type of Mesh will determine what Items are obtained from Sieving. \\n\\nOnce you have everything, automate the Blocks into the lFlux Sieve and it will put the Resources into the Inventory beneath it!]&f"]
	quest.7455D154FD1B4716.title: "&b&l&a通量筛子&f&7[lFlux Sieve]&f"
	quest.74C6A31F7D3E15CF.quest_desc: ["等等,为什么它做出了&7&a富集铁&f&r？\\n\\n哦,我们还需要用&0煤炭&r对&7&a富集铁&f&r进行&9灌注&r.这会给我们&8&a钢粉&f&r!\\n\\n熔炼&8&a钢粉&f&r,我们最终就能得到&8&a钢锭&f&r.\\n\\n我想你已经准备好迎接&5&l&d通用机械&f&r了!\\n&7[Wait, why did it make Enriched Iron? \\n\\nOh, we just need to Infuse the Enriched Iron with Coal as well. This will give us Steel Dust! \\n\\nSmelt the Steel Dust and we'll finally have Steel Ingots. \\n\\nI think you are ready to take on lMekanism then!]&f"]
	quest.74C6A31F7D3E15CF.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f&7[lMekanism]&f"
	quest.74CEF0D801DEE219.quest_desc: ["一旦&c&l熔铸厂&r开始冒烟,我们的材料开始熔化,我们就需要一个地方来放置它,以制造我们的&6地质矿石&r!\\n\\n&8&a铸造盆&f&r将非常完美,因为我们需要将价值一整个方块的锭浇铸到&e1 &a一重压缩沙子&f&r中,以制造一个&6地质矿石&r.\\n\\n将&e&a一重压缩沙子&f&r放入&8铸造盆&r中,然后在&8铸造盆&r上方的&b排液口&r上使用&7龙头&r,将材料输送进去.\\n\\n等待片刻让它冷却,我们现在应该就有了我们的...\\n&7[Once the lFoundry is smoking and our Materials are melting, we'll need a place to put it in order to make our GeOres! \\n\\nThe Casting Basin will be perfect as we need to Cast a full Block's worth of Ingot into 1 Compressed Sand in order to make a GeOre. \\n\\nPlace the Compressed Sand into the Basin, then use the Tap on a Drain above the Basin to deliver the Material into it. \\n\\nWait a second to let it cool off and we should now have our...]&f"]
	quest.76B5E884D18F5A7B.quest_desc: ["我不管你怎么弄到它们!去弄来就行!\\n\\n你可以使用工程师锤将 1 &a铁锭&f合成为 1 &a铁板&f,代价是消耗耐久度.\\n\\n你可以使用&a锻造锤&f,它可以将 2 &a铁锭&f变成 1 块板,或者如果你加入一个&8&lMI&r锤子,就只需要&a1 锭&f.\\n\\n见鬼,甚至&6&l铁路工艺&r也给了我们&a人力辊压机&f,但那只能将 4 &a铁锭&f变成 4 &a铁板&f.\\n&7[I don't care how you get them! Just get them! \\n\\nYou can use an Engineer's Hammer to Craft 1 Iron Ingot into 1 Iron Plate at the cost of Durability. \\n\\nYou can use a Forge Hammer which can turn 2 Iron Ingots into 1 Plate, or if you add in an lMI Hammer it will only need 1 Ingot. \\n\\nHeck, even lRailCraft gives us the Manual Rolling Machine but that can only turn 4 Iron Ingots into 4 Iron Plates.]&f"]
	quest.76B5E884D18F5A7B.title: "&a铁板&f&7[Iron Plates]&f"
	quest.7A7D7227BECE21B6.quest_desc: ["&5&l压印器&r是&b&l应用能源 2&r中使用的一种机器,不幸的是它需要能量才能工作...\\n\\n但如果我们确实有多余的能量,我们可以用它来转化物品!\\n\\n从锭和晶体变成粉末,到组合电路!\\n\\n要使用它,将物品放在左边的 3 个槽位中,如果有能量(并且配方正确),那么我们的产品就会出现在右边.\\n&7[The lInscriber is a Machine used in lAE2, which will unfortunately need Energy to work... \\n\\nBut if we do have Energy to spare we can use it to transform Items! \\n\\nFrom Ingots and Crystals to Dust, to combining Circuits! \\n\\nTo use it, place Items in the 3 Slots on the Left and if there is Energy (and a correct Recipe) then our Product will end up on the Right.]&f"]
	quest.7A7D7227BECE21B6.title: "&5&l压印器&7[lInscriber]&f"
	quest.7E8E9F1F6BE23268.quest_desc: [
		"现在我们有了方块,我们需要组装我们的&c&l熔铸厂&r.\\n\\n首先是&6液态加热线圈&r.这些将构成&c&l熔铸厂&r的地板,并且是加热&c&l熔铸厂&r所必需的.\\n\\n墙壁将由&c&a烈焰砖&f&r或窗户构成.墙壁也将是我们放置&b排液口&f、&4储罐&f和&a控制器&r的地方.\\n\\n&c&l熔铸厂&r不需要建造外框,所以每个角落都可以保持空着；但它必须有 4 面墙和一个地板才能完成.如果有缺失的方块,&a控制器&r会告诉你哪里缺失.\\n\\n&c&l熔铸厂&r的内部可以小到 1x1,只要它有一个&a控制器&r、&6液态加热线圈&r,并且其他墙壁都填满了!\\n\\n不过我不建议造这么小的,因为&c&l熔铸厂&r越大,里面的空间就越多!\\n\\n当&a控制器&r像熔炉一样亮起,并且&6液态加热线圈&r变成&6橙色&r时,你就知道&c&l熔铸厂&r建好了.\\n&7[Now that we have our Blocks we'll need to assemble our lFoundry. \\n\\nFirst, is Liquid Heating Coils. These will make up the floor of the lFoundry, and are needed to Heat up the lFoundry. \\n\\nThe Walls will be made of Fire Bricks or Windows. The Walls will also be where we place our Drains, Tanks, and Controllers. \\n\\nThe lFoundry will not need the frame built out, so every corner can remain empty; but it must have 4 Walls and a Floor to be completed. The Controller will tell you where a Block is missing, if there is one. \\n\\nThe lFoundry can be as small as 1x1 on the inside, as long as it has a Controller, Liquid Heating Coils, and the other Walls filled! \\n\\nI don't recommend making one so small though, as the bigger the lFoundry, the more space it has in it! \\n\\nYou'll know the lFoundry is built, when the Controller lights up like a Furnace, and the Liquid Heating Coils turn Orange.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap2/chap2_foundry.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.7E8E9F1F6BE23268.title: "&c&l熔铸厂&7[lFoundry]&f"
	task.18574AAEB6B01E23.title: "锤子&7[Hammers]&f"
	task.1EB84CB8EE502009.title: "&a熔铸炉控制器&f&7[Foundry Controllers]&f"
	task.2A6B52161759B041.title: "尖刺&7[Spikes]&f"
	task.2D99E799D705C751.title: "压印器压板&7[Inscriber Presses]&f"
	task.3ECD980426D48A3D.title: "8x 发电机&7[8x Generators]&f"
	task.40EA7B0CB21276E4.title: "64x 发电机&7[64x Generators]&f"
	task.48FBBB59246F4831.title: "熔铸厂墙壁&7[Foundry Walls]&f"
	task.5CD77BCA43DF7796.title: "熔铸厂储罐&7[Foundry Tanks]&f"
	task.5FA76A208C54EBBC.title: "熔铸厂排液口&7[Foundry Drains]&f"
	quest.0143D41FAD499FD0.quest_desc: ["不,我们不需要任何花哨的合成来制作&3振金升级模板&r.\\n\\n只需要普通的合成!\\n\\n制作你的第一个模板,你需要一个&6合金升级模板&r、7 个&6合金锭&r和一个&3&a块&f振金&r.\\n\\n其他的&3振金升级模板&r只需要另一个&3振金升级模板&r、7 个&6合金锭&r和&3&a远古石&f&r.\\n&7[No we won't need any fancy Crafting for the 振金 Upgrade Template. \\n\\nJust normal Crafting! \\n\\nTo make your first you'll need an AllTheModium Upgrade, 7 AllTheModium Ingots, and a Block of 振金. \\n\\nThe other 振金 Upgrades will only need another 振金 Upgrade, 7 AllTheModium Ingots, and Ancient Stone.]&f"]
	quest.0143D41FAD499FD0.title: "&3振金 &a锻造模板&f&7[振金 Smithing Template]&f"
	quest.03F381C22741F1E6.quest_desc: ["这里没有太多独特的变化,只是像往常一样更快更强!\\n&7[Not much unique change here, just faster and stronger per usual!]&f"]
	quest.052FDEEDAAC3F932.quest_desc: ["&3&a振金剑&f&r现在造成 36 &4点伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f为 3.6.\\n\\n&3&a振金斧&f&r造成 38 &4点伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f与&2&l原版&r斧相同,并且有 16 &a挖掘速度&f.\\n\\n从&6合金钉头锤&r升级到&3振金钉头锤&r需要花费一个&3&a块&f振金&r.&3振金&r钉头锤将造成 26 &4点伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f为 20.\\n\\n是的,钉头锤在坠落时会造成更多&a伤害&f.\\n&7[The 振金 Sword now does 36 Damage with a 3.6 Attack Speed. \\n\\nThe 振金 Axe does 38 Damage with same Attack Speed as lVanilla Axes, as well as 16 Mining Speed. \\n\\nIt will cost a Block of 振金 to Upgrade from AllTheModium Mace to 振金 Mace. The 振金 one will do 26 Damage with 20 Attack Speed. \\n\\nYes, Maces do more Damage while Falling.]&f"]
	quest.078C16A9D3BAEA45.quest_desc: ["使用&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r,我们可以制造&3&a远古石&f&r.\\n\\n我们需要&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r和一个&7&a石制发电机&f&r.\\n\\n我们可以在&7&a石制发电机&f&r的侧面使用&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r和&b&a浮冰&f&r,但我们需要在下方放置一个&6合金块&r.\\n\\n想要更便宜的选项？用&b&a蓝冰&f&r代替&b&a浮冰&f&r,你可以在下方放置一个&a氧化的 &a铜块&f&r.\\n&7[With Soul Lava we can make Ancient Stone. \\n\\nWe'll need Soul Lava and a Stone Generator. \\n\\nWe can use Soul Lava and Packed Ice on the Stone Generators sides, but we'll need an AllTheModium Block underneath. \\n\\nWant a cheaper option? Use Blue Ice instead of Packed Ice and you can place an Oxidized Copper Block below it. ]&f"]
	quest.078C16A9D3BAEA45.title: "&3&a古代石头&f&7[Ancient Stone]&f"
	quest.09EFBC2297441B77.quest_desc: ["什么？&c&a下界合金熔炉&f&r对你来说还不够吗!\\n\\n好吧,你可以把它们做成&6合金熔炉&r.\\n\\n它们的烹饪时间与&c&a下界合金熔炉&f&r相同,都是 5 游戏刻(0.25 秒),但&6合金熔炉&r一次可以烹饪 16 个物品.\\n\\n这意味着一整组物品会在一秒钟内熔炼完毕.\\n&7[What? Are Netherite Furnaces not enough for you! \\n\\nWell, you can make them into AllTheModium Furnaces. \\n\\nThey have the same Cooking Time as fNetherite Furnaces of 5 Ticks (0.25 seconds) but the AllTheModium Furnace Cooks Items at 16 at a time. \\n\\nThat means an entire Stack will be Smelt in a second.]&f"]
	quest.09EFBC2297441B77.title: "&6合金熔炉&7[AllTheModium Furnace]&f"
	quest.0DD626A1DB5A589F.quest_desc: ["&5&a难得素剑&f&r造成 51 &4点伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f为 4.4.三下就能杀死&d&l&a末影龙&f&r!\\n\\n&5&a难得素斧&f&r造成 51 &4点伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f为 1.2... 等等,这和&5剑&r一样？至少它有 18 &a挖掘速度&f.\\n\\n遵循同样的模式,我们需要一个&5&a难得块&f&r而不是&5锭&r.&5难得素钉头锤&r将造成 36 &4点伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f为 22.\\n&7[51 Damage and 4.4 Attack Speed from 难得素 Sword. That's 3 Hits to Kill the lEnder Dragon! \\n\\nThe 难得素 Axe does 51 Damage and 1.2 Attack Speed... wait that's the same as the Sword? Atleast it has 18 Mining Speed. \\n\\nFollowing the same pattern, we'll need an 难得素 Block instead of Ingot. The 难得素 Mace will do 36 Damage with a 22 Attack Speed.]&f"]
	quest.15672B8686426197.quest_desc: ["使用&3&a振金镐&f&r(或同等级工具),我们可以开采&5&a难得矿石&f&r!\\n\\n别忘了进行矿石处理!让你的钱花得最值!\\n&7[With a 振金 Pickaxe (or equivalent) we can Mine the 难得素 Ore! \\n\\nDon't forget to Ore Process it! Get the most bang for your buck! ]&f"]
	quest.15672B8686426197.title: "&5&l难得素&7[l难得素]&f"
	quest.17378FE70654852D.quest_desc: ["ME 无限单元在驱动器中的工作方式与普通单元类似,只是它们不存储物品,而是为你提供无限数量的那种物品!\\n\\n它们都需要&a256M-MEGA存储组件&f以及十亿个物品...好吧,不是十亿,但也差不多了.\\n\\n外加一个合金锭、振金锭和&a难得素锭&f.\\n&7[The ME infinity Cell work like normal Cells in a Drive, just instead of Storing Items, they will provide you an infinite amount of that Item! \\n\\nAll of them require the 256M MEGA Storage Component as well as a billion Items... okay not a billion but pretty close. \\n\\nPlus an AllTheModium, 振金, and 难得素 Ingot.]&f"]
	quest.17378FE70654852D.title: "&l无限 ME 单元&7[lInfinity ME Cells]&f"
	quest.19D9C6110D72EA7E.quest_desc: ["这是所有&b筛矿&r方块.\\n\\n&2苔藓 &f和&c&a红沙&f&r使用 5 重压缩,其他列出的所有方块都使用 6 重压缩.\\n&7[This is every Sieve Block. \\n\\nMoss and Red Sand use 5x Compressed and everything else listed uses 6x Compressed.]&f"]
	quest.19E8DD3B8554BF57.quest_desc: ["&5难得素升级模板&r遵循相同的模式.\\n\\n你需要一个&5&a块&f难得素&r、7 个&3&a振金锭&f&r和一个&3振金升级模板&r.\\n\\n你可以用另外 7 个&3&a振金锭&f&f和一个单独的&e末地石&r来复制它们!\\n&7[The 难得素 Upgrade follows the same pattern. \\n\\nYou'll need a Block of 难得素, 7 振金 Ingots, and a 振金 Upgrade Template. \\n\\nYou can duplicate them with another 7 振金 Ingots and a singular Endstone!]&f"]
	quest.19E8DD3B8554BF57.title: "&5难得素升级模板&7[难得素 Upgrade Template]&f"
	quest.208734A50051ECEC.quest_desc: [
		"就像将任何东西升级到&6合金&r一样,你需要一个&6合金锭&f和一个&6合金升级模板&r.\\n\\n你还需要一本&d大法师的法术书&r!\\n\\n&6合金 &d法术书&r将能够施放第 4 阶符文.不过,我们目前还没有任何那种符文...但它确实让我们每个法术最多可以使用 12 个符文.确保留意符文旁边的箭头,像这样:\\n&7[Like Upgrading anything to AllTheModium, you'll need an AllTheModium Ingot and AllTheModium Upgrade. \\n\\nYou'll just also need an Archmage's Spellbook! \\n\\nThe AllTheModium Spellbook will be able to Cast Tier 4 Glyphs. We don't exactly have any of those, though...it does let us use up to 12 glyphs per spell though. Make sure to keep an eye out for an arrow next to the Glyphs, like so:]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/chap3/spell_book_arrow.png width:300 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.208734A50051ECEC.title: "&6合金 &d&a法术书&f&7[AllTheModium Spell Book]&f"
	quest.21A953649550C761.quest_desc: ["&6合金工具&r是&c下界合金工具&r的升级版.\\n\\n它们更快、更强,而且无法破坏？是的,它们甚至没有耐久度!\\n\\n&6合金镐&r可以开采&c下界合金&r及以下等级无法开采的方块...&6锹&r和&6锄&r除了无法破坏和更快之外,没有新功能.\\n&7[AllTheModium Tools are an Upgrade to Netherite Tools. \\n\\nThese are faster, stronger, and Unbreakable? Yep, they don't even have Durability! \\n\\nThe AllTheModium Pickaxe can Mine Blocks Netherite and below can't... the Shovel and Hoe don't do anything new besides be Unbreakable and faster.]&f"]
	quest.225C6EB3287BC8A2.quest_desc: ["使用我们新发现的&b&a精英工作台&f&r,我们可以用 7x7 的网格来制作&b&a晶素锭&f&r!\\n\\n我们只需要 10 个&9&a青金石&f&r、8 个&b钻石&r、4 个&e金&r、4 个&7铁&r和 2 个&a下界之星&f来制作 4 个&b&a晶素锭&f&r.\\n\\n合成它需要一个特定的图案.\\n&7[With our new-found Elite Crafting Table we can use the 7x7 Grid to make Crystaltine Ingots! \\n\\nWe'll just need 10 Lapis Lazuli, 8 Diamonds, 4 Gold, 4 Iron, and 2 Nether Stars to make 4 Crystaltine Ingots. \\n\\nThere is a specific pattern you need to use to Craft it.]&f"]
	quest.225C6EB3287BC8A2.title: "&b&a晶素锭&f&7[Crystaltine Ingot]&f"
	quest.24CE75F2FA3F08C9.quest_desc: ["回到&a&a末影工作台&f&r!\\n\\n将&b&a晶素锭&f&r放在中间槽位,然后用一堆&7地质矿石碎片&r包围它.\\n\\n哪些&7碎片&r？就是石英、&7铁&r、&e金&r、&b钻石&r、&a绿宝石&r、&a铀&r和 2 个&2沥青铀矿&r!\\n\\n现在我们终于得到了&3振金&r.\\n&7[Back to the Ender Crafter! \\n\\nPut the Crystaltine Ingot in the middle slot then surround it with a bunch of GeOre Shards. \\n\\nWhich Shards? Just Quartz, Iron, Gold, Diamond, Emerald, Uranium, and 2 Uraninite! \\n\\nNow we finally got 振金. ]&f"]
	quest.24CE75F2FA3F08C9.title: "&3&l振金&7[l振金]&f"
	quest.258C1375A5DB4253.quest_desc: ["什么比&6合金&r更好？&3振金&r就是!\\n\\n&3&a振金熔炉&f&r的烹饪时间为 3 游戏刻,一次可以熔炼 32 个物品.\\n\\n一整组物品只需要 6 游戏刻!\\n&7[What's better than AllTheModium? 振金 is! \\n\\nThe 振金 Furnace has a Cooktime of 3 Ticks and will Smelt 32 Items at a time. \\n\\nAn entire Stack of Items in 6 Ticks!]&f"]
	quest.258C1375A5DB4253.title: "&3&a振金熔炉&f&7[振金 Furnace]&f"
	quest.2A9F546586CAC34E.quest_desc: ["任何&d&l奥术&r玩家所能要求的最好装备!\\n\\n40 &a护甲值&f但只有 24 &a盔甲韧性&f,最糟糕的是...没有&a击退抗性&f.\\n\\n至少我们确实获得了更多的法力和&a法术强度&f!\\n&7[The best any lArs Player can ask for! \\n\\n40 Armor Points but only 24 Armor Toughness and worst of all... no Knockback Resistance. \\n\\nAtleast we do get even more Mana and Spell Power!]&f"]
	quest.2BC31E5B6BD68A35.quest_desc: ["现在能够在一个法术中使用 15 个符文.\\n&7[Now able to use 15 Glyphs in one spell.]&f"]
	quest.2BC31E5B6BD68A35.title: "&3振金 &d&a法术书&f&7[振金 Spell Book]&f"
	quest.2C2BF70590DBF943.quest_desc: ["&a&a末影工作台&f&r,尽管看起来像工作台,但大不相同!\\n\\n制作它和&a&a末影发电机&f&r非常简单.需要工作台、&a末影之眼&r和&2&a末影锭&f&r.这些只是&a&a末影珍珠&f&r和&7铁锭&r.\\n\\n说到&a末影发电机&r,我们需要在一个7x7x7的区域内放置一个,并将&a&a末影工作台&f&r放在中心.\\n&7[The Ender Crafter is, despite looking like a Crafting Table, much different! \\n\\nCrafting it and the Ender Alternator is pretty simple. Crafting Table, Eyes of Ender, and Ender Ingots. Those are just Ender Pearls and Iron. \\n\\nSpeaking of the Alternator, we will need one in a 7x7x7 Area with the Ender Crafter in the center.  ]&f"]
	quest.2C2BF70590DBF943.title: "&a&a末影工作台&f&7[Ender Crafter]&f"
	quest.2D7FCB751FC563E5.quest_desc: ["&5不可得合金盔甲&r拥有所有盔甲中最高的&a护甲值&f和盔甲韧性!只是防护值不如量子盔甲或MekaSuit.\\n\\n它提供40点&a护甲值&f和60点&a盔甲韧性&f.外加100%的&a击退抗性&f!没人能告诉你该往哪走.\\n\\n现在,加上之前盔甲提供的其他效果,我们将获得90%的&d魔法&a伤害抵抗&f&r.\\n\\n而且说真的,这绝对是最好看的盔甲套装!\\n&7[难得素 Armor has the highest Armor Points and Toughness of any Armor! Just not more Protection than Quantum Armor or MekaSuit. \\n\\nWith 40 Armor Points and 60 Armor Toughness. Plus 100% Knockback Resistance! Nobody will tell you where to go.\\n\\nNow, along with the other effects given by the previous Armors, we'll get 90% Magic Damage Resistance.\\n\\nAnd I mean come on, it is easily the best looking Armor Set!]&f"]
	quest.2D7FCB751FC563E5.title: "&5不可得合金盔甲&7[难得素 Armor]&f"
	quest.31C384EB37DD24BC.quest_desc: ["我们得到两把常规武器,外加一把(算是)新的&8钉锤&r!\\n\\n这把&6剑&r造成18点&4伤害&r,&a攻击速度&f为2.6.比&2&l原版&r剑的1.6快多了!\\n\\n这把&6斧&r既可以当工具也可以当武器!它可以附魔&a效率&f和锋利.&6全模合金斧&r造成22点&4伤害&r,但&a攻击速度&f为0.8...比普通斧头1点的&a攻击速度&f要慢.\\n\\n&6钉锤&r是&2&l原版Minecraft&r最新的武器,所以我们当然要搞一个&6全模合金&r版本!\\n\\n不过首先,你需要一把&8钉锤&r.要获得它们,你需要召唤一只狂野微风来获取&7&a旋风棒&f&r.然后,用那些&7&a旋风棒&f&r你可以召唤一只狂野微风来获取&a试炼钥匙&f.用那些钥匙你最终可以召唤一只强壮的狂野微风来获得我们的&8&a沉重核心&f&r.\\n\\n要升级它,我们需要一个&6全模合金升级&r和一个&6&a块&f全模合金&r.这把&6钉锤&r将有13点&4伤害&r和19点&a攻击速度&f!是的,你从越高的地方落下,它造成的&a伤害&f就越高.\\n&7[We get the 2 usual Weapons, plus the (kinda) new Mace! \\n\\nThe Sword does 18 Damage with a 2.6 Attack Speed. Much faster than the lVanilla Swords at 1.6! \\n\\nThe Axe can be used as a Tool and Weapon! It can take Efficiency and Sharpness. The AllTheModium Axe does 22 Damage, but with an Attack Speed of 0.8... Slower than normal Axes at 1 Attack Speed. \\n\\nThe Mace is the newest Weapon to lVanilla Minecraft so of course we get an AllTheModium version! \\n\\nFirst though, you'll need a Mace. To get them, you'll need to summon a Wild Breeze to get Breeze Rods. Then, with those Breeze Rods you can summon a Wild Breeze to get Trial Keys. With those Keys you can finally summon a Strong Wild Breeze to get our Heavy Core. \\n\\nTo Upgrade it we'll need an AllTheModium Upgrade and a Block of AllTheModium. The Mace will have 13 Damage with a 19 Attack Speed! And yes, it does more Damage the higher you fall from.]&f"]
	quest.337022C12CE5FD07.quest_desc: ["要养殖&6ATM合金&r,你首先需要一些&c&a远古蜜蜂&f&r.我说一些是因为你需要它们的&c&a刷怪蛋&f&r.\\n\\n这意味着你需要用一堆&c&a下界合金块&f&r喂给&b&a钻石蜜蜂&f&r.\\n\\n一旦你获得一个&c&a远古蜜蜂&f &a刷怪蛋&f&r.使用&c&l铸造厂&r将4个&6ATM合金锭&r浇铸到&c&a刷怪蛋&f&r上,以创建一个&6ATM合金蜜蜂 &a刷怪蛋&f&r.\\n\\n别以为这就是你需要花费的唯一&6ATM合金&r!你还需要一个&6&a块&f ATM合金&r作为&6蜜蜂&r的&6&a繁花方块&f&r.\\n&7[To Farm AllTheModium you'll first need some Ancient Bees. I say some because you'll need a Spawn Egg of them. \\n\\nThat means you'll need to use a bunch of Netherite Blocks to feed to Diamond Bees. \\n\\nOnce you get an Ancient Bee Spawn Egg. Use the lFoundry to pour 4 AllTheModium Ingots onto the Spawn Egg to create an AllTheModium Bee Spawn Egg. \\n\\nDon't think that's the only AllTheModium you'll need to spend! You'll also need a Block of AllTheModium to be a Flowering Block to the Bee.]&f"]
	quest.337022C12CE5FD07.title: "&6ATM合金蜜蜂&7[AllTheModium Bee]&f"
	quest.38256909C87DCD36.quest_desc: ["&dATM奥术师装备&r的制作方式与&6ATM合金&r类似,只是不是升级&c下界合金&r,而是升级&2地脉&f/&b天域&f/&b水脉&f/&c火脉&r法师&d装备&r.\\n\\n这些装备会提供24点&a护甲值&f,但只有16点&a盔甲韧性&f,且没有&a击退抗性&f.\\n\\n它通过提供更多的最大魔力、&a魔力再生&f和&a法术强度&f来弥补!\\n\\n它还几乎继承了&6ATM合金盔甲&r提供的所有额外增益.\\n&7[AllTheArcanist Gear is created similar to AllTheModium, just instead of Upgrading Netherite, you'll Upgrade the Geo/Aether/Aqua/Pyro-mancer Gear. \\n\\nThese will give 24 Armor Points but only 16 Armor Toughness and no Knockback Resistance. \\n\\nIt makes up for it by giving more Max Mana, Mana Regen, and Spell Power!\\n\\nIt also carries almost all of the extra buffs AllTheModium Armor offers.]&f"]
	quest.3D4CCEA2ED727AE4.quest_desc: ["要获得我们所有的&6ATM合金装备&r,我们需要:&6ATM合金锭&r、&6ATM合金锻造模板&r和&c&a下界合金齿轮&f&r(或者对应模组的最佳装备,例如&d奥术师装备&r).\\n&7[To get all of our AllTheModium Gear, we'll need: AllTheModium Ingot, AllTheModium Upgrade Template, and Netherite Gear (or the Mods best gear like for the Arcanist Gear).]&f"]
	quest.3D4CCEA2ED727AE4.title: "&6ATM合金锻造模板&7[AllTheModium Upgrade Template]&f"
	quest.4AEA51A241D61D15.quest_desc: ["通过挤压和组合足够多的&a恶魂蜜蜂&f,我们可以制作一个&a恶魂蜜蜂&f &a刷怪蛋&f.\\n\\n使用&c&l铸造厂&r将一桶量的&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r浇铸到它上面,我们将得到一个&9&a灵魂熔岩蜜蜂&f&r!\\n\\n这只&9蜜蜂&r将使用&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r作为其&6&a繁花方块&f&r.别担心,它们是&a火焰免疫生物&f!\\n\\n不过其他蜜蜂可能不是……也许把这些家伙单独放在一个区域里……\\n&7[By squishing and combining enough Ghostly Bees we can make a Ghostly Bee Spawn Egg. \\n\\nBy pouring a Buckets worth of Soul Lava onto it with the lFoundry, we will get a Soul Lava Bee! \\n\\nThis Bee will use Soul Lava as its Flowering Block. Don't worry they're Fire Resistant! \\n\\nOther Bees might not be though... maybe keep these guys in their own sections...]&f"]
	quest.4AEA51A241D61D15.title: "&9&a灵魂熔岩蜜蜂&f&7[Soul Lava Bee]&f"
	quest.4D525B47CCCAC0B3.quest_desc: ["你已经知道如何获得一个&6ATM合金 &a刷怪蛋&f&r了,所以我们直接切入正题!\\n\\n只需将4个&3&a振金锭&f&r浇铸到一个&6ATM合金 &a刷怪蛋&f&r上.\\n\\n你需要一个&3&a振金块&f&r作为&6&a繁花方块&f&r.\\n\\n就这样!\\n&7[You already know how to get an AllTheModium Spawn Egg, so let's cut straight to the point! \\n\\nJust pour 4 振金 Ingots over an AllTheModium Spawn Egg. \\n\\nYou'll need a 振金 Block as a Flowering Block. \\n\\nThat's it!]&f"]
	quest.4D525B47CCCAC0B3.title: "&3&a振金蜜蜂&f&7[振金 Bee]&f"
	quest.4D96FBB5645ADC84.quest_desc: ["有些玩家宁愿使用能量而不是燃料.唯一的问题是&c供能加热线圈&r只能让我们达到1500°C.\\n\\n哦等等,有解决办法!&b高功率加热线圈&r!\\n\\n这将允许我们使用能量并达到3000°C.\\n&7[Some Players would rather use Energy than Fuel. Only problem is that the Powered Heating Coils will only get us 1500 C. \\n\\nOh wait, there is a solution! High Powered Heating Coils! \\n\\nThis will allow us to use Energy and get up to 3000 C.]&f"]
	quest.4D96FBB5645ADC84.title: "&b高功率加热线圈&7[High Powered Heating Coil]&f"
	quest.5319D267A6A2C625.quest_desc: ["所有16种&2&l原版&r &c染&e色&a剂&b&r!抱歉&l&c染&6色&e剂&a&b&9&5&d&c&r,那些必须合成.\\n\\n你需要6个同色压缩混凝土来制作对应的&c染&e色&b剂&r.\\n&7[All the 16 lVanilla Dyes! Sorry lDyenamics, those will have to be Crafted. \\n\\nYou'll need 6x Compressed Concrete for the same Color Dye.]&f"]
	quest.5319D267A6A2C625.title: "无限&c染&e色&a剂&b&7[Infinite Dyes]&f"
	quest.538C9CDF7BEC18D8.quest_desc: ["每一个符文!全部!!!\\n\\n\\n\\n都可以使用.你可以在一个法术中使用多达20个.\\n&7[Every single Glyph! EVER!!! \\n\\n\\n\\nIs available. You can use up to 20 in one spell.]&f"]
	quest.538C9CDF7BEC18D8.title: "&5难得素 &d&a法术书&f&7[难得素 Spell Book]&f"
	quest.53A6BC88439B6767.quest_desc: ["&6ATM合金&r由&6粒&r制成,你需要9个&6ATM合金粒&r来制作1个&6锭&r.\\n\\n你最初获得&6粒&r的方式是通过&b&l筛矿&r.\\n\\n你需要&a钻石筛网&f或&a下界合金筛网&f,下界合金筛网有更高的几率.\\n\\n你可以&b&l筛&r &0粉碎黑石&r或&e沙子&r.&0黑石&r掉落&6ATM合金&r的几率更高!\\n&7[AllTheModium is created from the Nuggets, you'll need a 9 Piece AllTheModium Nuggets to make 1 Ingot. \\n\\nThe way you originally get the Nugget is from lSieving. \\n\\nYou'll need either a Diamond Mesh or Netherite Mesh, with Netherite giving higher chances. \\n\\nAnd you can lSieve Crushed Blackstone or Sand. With Blackstone having higher chances of Dropping AllTheModium!]&f"]
	quest.53A6BC88439B6767.title: "&l第三章:&6ATM合金&7[lChapter 3: AllTheModium]&f"
	quest.54A9C70D01935A16.quest_desc: ["遵循相同的模式,将4个&a难得素锭&f浇铸到一个&a振金蜜蜂&f &a刷怪蛋&f上.\\n\\n并使用一个&a叵得块&f作为&6&a繁花方块&f&r.\\n\\n砰!基本上是免费的难得素!\\n&7[Follow the same pattern, pour 4 难得素 Ingots over a 振金 Bee Spawn Egg. \\n\\nAnd use an 难得素 Block as a Flowering Block. \\n\\nBoom! Basically free 难得素!]&f"]
	quest.54A9C70D01935A16.title: "&5&a难得素蜜蜂&f&7[难得素 Bee]&f"
	quest.55E56A748C8681AC.quest_desc: ["我把剩下的无限单元都扔在这里了……\\n\\n它包括&7黏土&r、&0基岩&r、&b&a陨石&f&r和&3&a古代石头&f&r.\\n\\n全部需要5倍压缩.\\n&7[I just threw the rest of the Infinite Cells here... \\n\\nIt has Clay, Kivi, Sky Stone, and Ancient Stone. \\n\\nAll require 5x Compressed.]&f"]
	quest.55E56A748C8681AC.title: "无限杂项方块&7[Infinite ETC Blocks]&f"
	quest.5663FA8B7C8570C5.quest_desc: ["别担心,我们仍然可以通过传统方式获得&5难得素&r!\\n\\n是的,就在这些古老的&d末地高地&r里.\\n&7[Don't worry, we still get 难得素 through the old fashioned way! \\n\\nYep, right here in them ole End Highlands.]&f"]
	quest.5663FA8B7C8570C5.title: "&d&l末地&7[lThe End]&f"
	quest.589A36B5AEC1E588.quest_desc: ["&6ATM合金 &d奥术师装备&r的&a新材料发现&f是&3振金 &d奥术师装备&r.\\n\\n它仍然像&3振金&r一样提供32点&a护甲值&f,但像&6ATM合金 &d奥术师装备&r一样,它不提供那么多&a盔甲韧性&f(20)或&a击退抗性&f(0).\\n\\n相反,它会提供最大魔力、&a魔力再生&f和&a法术强度&f!甚至比&6ATM合金&r那套给的还要多!\\n&7[The Upgrade to AllTheModium Arcanist Gear is 振金 Arcanist Gear. \\n\\nIt still gives 32 Armor Points like 振金, but like the AllTheModium Arcanist Gear it doesn't give as much Armor Toughness (20) or Knockback Resistance (0). \\n\\nInstead it will give Max Mana, Mana Regen, and Spell Power! Even more than what the AllTheModium one gives!]&f"]
	quest.5A21264D1043A0DA.quest_desc: ["这些是与&b筛矿&r无关的&7石头&r!\\n\\n如果你打算用它们建造,会非常有帮助.\\n\\n除了使用6倍压缩的&7玄武岩&r外,其他都使用5倍压缩.\\n&7[These are the Stones that aren't related to Sieving! \\n\\nVery helpful if you plan on building out of them. \\n\\nAll of them use 5x Compressed besides Basalt which uses 6x.]&f"]
	quest.615CE400A733C804.quest_desc: ["现在我们可以合成我们的&6ATM合金锭&r了!\\n\\n它本身没什么大用……\\n\\n我们可以在&c&l铸造厂&r中熔炼它,然后浇铸到一个&c&a远古蜜蜂&f&r上,以开始自动化生产&6ATM合金&r.\\n\\n或者用它的一个&6块&r来制作一个&6ATM合金 &a锻造模板&f&r.别担心,在制作第一个之后,你可以用&c&a下界合金锭堆&f&r和&8深板岩&r来复制它.\\n&7[Now we can Craft our AllTheModium Ingot! \\n\\nWhich will not do much on its own... \\n\\nWe can Smelt it in a lFoundry and poor it over an Ancient Bee to start Automating AllTheModium. \\n\\nOr use a Block of it to make an AllTheModium Smithing Template. Don't worry after the first one, you can duplicate it with Netherite Ingots and Deepslate.]&f"]
	quest.615CE400A733C804.title: "&6&lATM合金&7[lAllTheModium]&f"
	quest.63BF3A8C26F37498.quest_desc: [
		"&b&a精英工作台&f&r是&8&l&d合成拓展&f&r的第三级.\\n\\n它有一个7x7的网格,我们需要它来合成&b&a晶素锭&f&r.\\n\\n要制作这个工作台,我们需要2个&e高级合成台&r.每个&e高级合成台&r需要2个基础合成台.\\n&7[The Elite Crafting Table is the third Tier of lExtended Crafting. \\n\\nIt has a 7x7 Grid which we'll need for Crafting the Crystaltine Ingot. \\n\\nTo make this Table, we'll need 2 Advanced Crafting Tables. Each of those will need 2 Basic Crafting Tables.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"算一下,你需要8个合成台、4个&7铁块&r、4个&8&a黑铁板&f&r、16个基础组件和4个基础催化剂.所有这些用来制作4个基础合成台.\\n\\n对于&e高级合成台&r,你将使用4个基础合成台、2个&e金块&r、2个&8&a黑铁板&f&r、8个&e高级组件&r和2个&e高级催化剂&r.\\n\\n最后,用这2个&e高级合成台&r,你可以将它们与一个&b钻石块&r、一个&8&a黑铁板&f&r、4个&b精英组件&r和1个&b精英催化剂&r组合.\\n&7[Doing the Math, you'll need 8 Crafting Tables, 4 Iron Blocks, 4 Black Iron Slates, 16 Basic Components, and 4 Basic Catalysts. All for 4 Basic Crafting Tables. \\n\\nFor the Advanced Crafting Tables you'll use the 4 Basic Crafting Tables, 2 Blocks of Gold, 2 Black Iron Slates, 8 Advanced Components, and 2 Advanced Catalysts. \\n\\nFinally with the 2 Advanced Crafting Tables you can combine them with a Diamond Block, a Black Iron Slate, 4 Elite Components, and 1 Elite Catalyst.]&f"
	]
	quest.63BF3A8C26F37498.quest_subtitle: "第三级&7[Tier 3]&f"
	quest.63BF3A8C26F37498.title: "&b&a精英工作台&f&7[Elite Crafting Table]&f"
	quest.6599BB9DCA903F65.quest_desc: ["只有你能想象到的最好的&5熔炉&r!\\n\\n&5&a难得素熔炉&f&r只需1游戏刻就能烧炼完成.二十分之一秒!\\n\\n而且它一次能烧炼一整组物品.\\n&7[Only the best Furnace imaginable! \\n\\nThe 难得素 Furnaces Cooks in only 1 Tick. 1/20th a second! \\n\\nAnd it Cooks them an entire Stack at a time.]&f"]
	quest.6599BB9DCA903F65.title: "&5&a难得素熔炉&f&7[难得素 Furnace]&f"
	quest.665980EC12F695E9.quest_desc: ["要获得&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r,我们需要一大堆&l&d工业先锋&f&r机器.\\n\\n首先,我们需要囚禁一个&3&l监守者&r(多么讽刺).使用并供能一个&8&a冷凝室&f&r来获得减速场.然后,把一个&3&l监守者&r弄进去.\\n\\n有很多方法可以获得&3&l监守者&r,特别是通过&3&a幽匿尖啸体&f&r和&3幽匿核心&r.\\n\\n然后,我们需要&b&a流体镭射钻基座&f&r直接放在&3&l监守者&r上方.在&b&a流体镭射钻基座&f&r中放置一个&9&a蓝色透镜&f&r,这是必须的!\\n\\n最后,我们需要&a镭射钻&f对准&b&a流体镭射钻基座&f&r,并且供能.然后,我们就会慢慢得到&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r!\\n&7[To get Soul Lava we need a whole lot of lIndustrial Foregoing Machines. \\n\\nFirst, we need to jail a lWarden (how ironic). Use and Power a Stasis Chamber to get the slow field. Then, get a lWarden into it. \\n\\nThere's a bunch of ways to get a lWarden especially through Sculk Shriekers with Sculk Cores. \\n\\nThen, we'll need the Fluid Laser Base directly above the lWarden. Place a Blue Lens in the Fluid Laser Base, it is necessary! \\n\\nLastly we'll need Laser Drills facing the Fluid Laser Base, and are Powered. Then, we will slowly get Soul Lava!]&f"]
	quest.665980EC12F695E9.title: "制作&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&7[Making Soul Lava]&f"
	quest.69AD0D65488065A4.quest_desc: ["&c下界合金&r的盔甲不够用？为什么不试试&6ATM合金&r!\\n\\n它的每一项属性都更高!并且无法破坏!\\n\\n24点&a护甲值&f,20点&a盔甲韧性&f,以及50%&a击退抗性&f.\\n\\n另外你还可以在上面使用盔甲纹饰!\\n\\n什么,你以为这就是全部了？\\n\\n&6头盔&r:&a&9水下呼吸&f&r、&a免疫&f &3&l监守者&r的&0黑暗效果&r,并且&7鞘翅&r不会造成&a伤害&f.\\n&6胸甲&r:50% &d魔法 &a伤害抵抗&f&r和&c&a火焰保护&f&r.\\n&6护腿&r:&9&a深海探索&f&r和&a免疫&f &0凋零&r效果.\\n&6靴子&r:抵抗&a摔落伤害&f,让你可以在&b细雪&r和&c熔岩&r上行走.\\n&7[Not enough Armor with Netherite? Why not use AllTheModium! \\n\\nIt is higher in every single statistic! And is Unbreakable! \\n\\n24 Armor Points, 20 Armor Toughness, and 50% Knockback Resistance. \\n\\nPlus you can use Trims on it!\\n\\nWhat, you think that's all they give?\\n\\nHelmets: Water Breathings, Immunity to lWarden Darkness Effect, and no Elytra Damage. \\nChestplate: 50% Magic Damage Resistance and Fire Resistance. \\nLeggings: Depth Strider and Immunity to Wither. \\nBoots: Resist Fall Damage, let you walk on Powdered Snow and Lava.]&f"]
	quest.69AD0D65488065A4.title: "&6ATM合金盔甲&7[AllTheModium Armor]&f"
	quest.6B04292F127FC8CB.quest_desc: ["&3振金盔甲套装&r拥有比&6ATM合金&r更好的属性.\\n\\n我们获得32点&a护甲值&f,36点&a盔甲韧性&f,以及80%&a击退抗性&f!\\n\\n不幸的是,我们没有获得新的效果和能力……但我们获得了更多的&d魔法 &a伤害抵抗&f&r!现在达到75%!\\n&7[The 振金 Armor Set has even better stats than AllTheModium. \\n\\nWe get 32 Armor Points, 36 Armor Toughness, and 80% Knockback Resistance!\\n\\nUnfortunately we don't get new effects and abilities... but we get more Magic Damage Resistance! Now at 75%!]&f"]
	quest.6B04292F127FC8CB.title: "&3振金盔甲&7[振金 Armor]&f"
	quest.6F37F7ABBBA910B2.quest_desc: ["一旦我们最终获得1000mB的&9&a灵魂熔岩&f&r,我们就可以把它装进一个&7桶&r里!从这里我们有很多选择.\\n\\n我们可以按照接下来的任务获取配方,用它作为&c坩埚&r或&6&a热力发电机&f&r的&6&a热源&f&r,或者把它扔进&c岩浆发电机&r!\\n\\n选择权在你,但我推荐获得一只&9&a灵魂熔岩蜜蜂&f&r.\\n&7[Once we finally get 1,000mB of Soul Lava we can put it into a Bucket! From here we got a lot of choices. \\n\\nWe can follow the next Quests for Recipes, use it as a Heat Source for Crucibles or Thermo Generators, or toss it into a Magmator! \\n\\nThe choice is yours, but I recommend getting a Soul Lava Bee.]&f"]
	quest.6F37F7ABBBA910B2.title: "&9&l&a灵魂熔岩&f&7[lSoul Lava]&f"
	quest.6F930E97EB804F15.quest_desc: ["&3&a振金锭&f&r需要数量惊人的&7地脉矿石&r.\\n\\n大多数都很简单,只需通过&c&l铸造厂&r将那种&7矿石&r覆盖在&e&a一重压缩沙子&f&r上……但&2沥青铀矿&r不同.\\n\\n我们需要使用我们的&a&a末影工作台&f&r将4个&2沥青铀矿&r与一个&a萌芽铀地脉矿石&r组合.\\n\\n你可以&b&l筛&r &e沙子&r,使用钻石或&a下界合金筛网&f来获得&2沥青铀矿&r!\\n&7[The 振金 Ingot needs an uncomfortable amount of GeOres. \\n\\nMost are pretty simple, just cover Compressed Sand with that Ore through the lFoundry... Uraninite is different though. \\n\\nWe'll need to use our Ender Crafter to combine 4 Uraninite with a Budding Uranium Geore. \\n\\nYou can lSieve Sand with a Diamond or Netherite Mesh to get Uraninite!]&f"]
	quest.6F930E97EB804F15.title: "&2沥青铀矿地脉矿石&7[Uraninite GeOre]&f"
	quest.737A779F82686366.quest_desc: ["当你可以制作零食时,为什么要把&6ATM合金&r用在&6工具&r和&6盔甲&r这些不必要的东西上呢!\\n\\n&6ATM合金胡萝卜&r将提供20点&a饥饿值&f.这相当于5块牛排!它还提供160点&a饱和度&f.这略高于21个&e&a金胡萝卜&f&r!\\n你很长一段时间都不用担心感到饥饿.\\n\\n&6ATM合金苹果&r提供的较少,只有10点&a饥饿值&f和40点&a饱和度&f.\\n\\n那么为什么要制作和食用&6苹果&r呢？也许是因为它能提供生命恢复和伤害吸收!\\n&7[Why use that AllTheModium on unnecessary stuff, like Tools and Armor, when you can make Snacks! \\n\\nThe AllTheModium Carrot will give 20 Food Points. That's equal to 5 Steaks! It also gives 160 Saturation Points. That's slightly over 21 Golden Carrots! \\nYou won't have to worry about feeling Hungry for a long time. \\n\\nThe AllTheModium Apple gives less, with only 10 Hunger Points and 40 Saturation Points. \\n\\nSo why make and Eat the Apple instead? Maybe because it gives Regeneration and Absorption!]&f"]
	quest.737A779F82686366.title: "&6ATM合金&r食物？&7[AllTheModium Food?]&f"
	quest.7DE7E266A42E822E.quest_desc: ["&3&a振金镐&f&r将用于开采&5不可得合金&r.\\n\\n&3锹&f和&3锄&r只是让它们的工作更快.\\n\\n嗯,我的意思是&3镐&r也一样,只是它更独特!\\n&7[The 振金 Pickaxe will be needed to Mine 难得素. \\n\\nThe Shovel and Hoe just do their job quicker. \\n\\nWell I mean the Pickaxe does as well, it's just more unique!]&f"]
	task.2954E9A84730D187.title: "&6全模合金武器&7[AllTheModium Weapons]&f"
	task.2FCC2AAD26F80D20.title: "&6全模合金&d奥术装备&7[AllTheModium Arcanist Gear]&f"
	task.3A705CAF7547846A.title: "无限&7石头&7[Infinite Stones]&f"
	task.44B02FBFAD918254.title: "ME无限染料单元&7[ME Infinity Dye Cells]&f"
	task.464877B75929C3C4.title: "&5不可得合金工具&7[难得素 Tools]&f"
	task.51CB2D73F130E55A.title: "&5不可得合金武器&7[难得素 Weapons]&f"
	task.5C5BD15346C75F38.title: "无限&b筛方块&7[Infinite Sieve Blocks]&f"
	task.6C22DF8825A25915.title: "&3振金工具&7[振金 Tools]&f"
	task.6EAD7AAB2A57424E.title: "&3振金武器&7[振金 Weapons]&f"
	task.6EFE20C8ED04A071.title: "&5不可得合金&d奥术装备&7[难得素 Arcanist Gear]&f"
	task.7226040F3B42C6E1.title: "&3振金&d奥术装备&7[振金 Arcanist Gear]&f"
	task.7F534695D6EC391F.title: "&6全模合金工具&7[AllTheModium Tools]&f"
	quest.3C12F07F989B108C.quest_subtitle: "一些聪明的玩意儿&7[something something smart stuff]&f"
	quest.3C8053A161AC5AA1.quest_subtitle: "粗略估计&7[Guestimates]&f"
	quest.3F21BA221276B4A4.quest_subtitle: "这不是曲奇&7[This is not a cookie]&f"
	quest.504DEB70D9DAA547.quest_desc: ["好吧,你做到了.我想说我曾持怀疑态度,但你做到了.\\n&7[Well, you got it. I wanna say I was skeptical but you got it.]&f"]
	quest.504DEB70D9DAA547.quest_subtitle: "恭喜!&7[Congratulations!]&f"
	quest.504DEB70D9DAA547.title: "&#FFDA59&aATM之星&f&7[&#FFDA59ATM Star]&f"
	quest.26B0D931730C13C2.quest_desc: [ ]
	quest.26B0D931730C13C2.quest_subtitle: ""
	quest.26B0D931730C13C2.title: "终结的开始&7[Beginning Of The End]&f"
	quest.26DF04FB3185ACDB.quest_desc: ["这将提供你所需要的&o所有&a气压&f&r,当然,这不是双关语.\\n&7[This will provide All The Pressure you could ever need, no pun intended of course.]&f"]
	quest.315F60A6F85B20C6.quest_subtitle: "法术即生命&7[Spells for life]&f"
	quest.3D4647F929C44E7E.quest_subtitle: "用这个你真的可以飞驰&7[You can really zoom with this one]&f"
	quest.541FAAC70253D519.quest_subtitle: "满足你魔法需求的一罐果汁&7[A jar of juice for your magical needs]&f"
	quest.69416C5D8EAD2C82.quest_subtitle: "按需温度控制&7[Temperature control as you need]&f"
	quest.74B8E2EA0BB98B5F.quest_desc: [ ]
	quest.74B8E2EA0BB98B5F.quest_subtitle: "把星块喂给蜜蜂&7[Feed the star block to the bee]&f"
	quest.74B8E2EA0BB98B5F.title: "&#7A95FF无限能量&7[&#7A95FFUnlimited Power]&f"
	quest.77E461E7705E4346.quest_desc: [ ]
	quest.77E461E7705E4346.quest_subtitle: "低调但有用的炫耀&7[Subtle flex that has a use]&f"
	quest.77E461E7705E4346.title: ""
	quest.78BCB80016523F07.quest_desc: ["这可以作为你&#7AFFFAAE&r系统的创造模式能源.\\n&7[This acts as a creative source for your &#7AFFFAAE system.]&f"]
	quest.0759CA52EECF3B49.quest_desc: ["&6&a动力犁&f&r会犁开它前进道路上的一切!嗯,至少是它能移动的东西.\\n\\n连接不牢固的方块在&6犁&r撞击时会立即破裂.例如火把、按钮和藤蔓这类方块.\\n\\n当在泥土或草方块上方使用时,它会造出耕地!非常适合建造巨型农场!\\n\\n你也可以用&6犁&r来移动生物而不杀死它们.嗯,&6犁&r本身不会杀死它们,但它们撞到的东西可能会.\\n&7[The Mechanical Plough will plough through anything in its way! Well, that it can move atleast. \\n\\nBlocks with weak connections will immediately break when the Plough hits them. Blocks like Torches, Buttons, and Vines. \\n\\nWhen used above Dirt or Grass, it will make Farmland! Perfect for Mega-Farms! \\n\\nYou can also use the Plough to move Mobs without killing them. Well the Plough won't kill them, whatever they hit might.]&f"]
	quest.0759CA52EECF3B49.title: "&6&a动力犁&f&7[Mechanical Plough]&f"
	quest.078C5B50CDC174CB.quest_desc: ["&a&a动力轴承&f&r是&a机械装置&r运动中最简单的形式.\\n\\n当从底部获得&d旋转动力&r时,它们会以相同的速度和方向旋转其上方的所有方块.\\n方块会自动&a粘合&r到&a&a动力轴承&f&r上,但任何其他方块也需要&a粘合&r到该方块上才能随之移动!\\n\\n如果你在&a机械装置&r内部使用&a&a动力轴承&f&r,它会尝试让&a粘合&f的部分保持静止,而不是旋转.\\n&7[Mechanical Bearings are the most simple forms of Contraption movement. \\n\\nWhen given Rotational Power from their bottom, they will rotate any Blocks above at the same Speed and Direction. \\nBlocks will automatically be Glued to the Mechanical Bearing, but any other Blocks will need to be Glued to that Block to move as well! \\n\\nIf you use a Mechanical Bearing within a Contraption itself, it will try and keep the Block attached still instead of Rotating.]&f"]
	quest.078C5B50CDC174CB.title: "&a&a动力轴承&f&7[Mechanical Bearing]&f"
	quest.087F6C09CB5B2D1A.quest_desc: ["&b&a智能流体管道&f&r将为&b&a流体传输管道&f&r提供过滤功能.\\n\\n当将其放置在&b管道&r正在抽取的机器上时,可以设置为只抽出一种&b流体&r.这通过在&a过滤槽位&f中放入一桶该&b液体&r来设置.\\n\\n你也可以将&b&a智能流体管道&f&r放置在&b管道系统&r的后面,以便只让特定的&b流体&r通过其后的&b管道&r.\\n\\n这对于大量分类一堆&b&a流体储罐&f&r很有帮助!\\n&7[Smart Fluid Pipes will give us Filtering for Fluid Pipes. \\n\\nWhen put on the Machine that the Pipes are extracting from, it can be set to only take out the one Fluid. This is set by adding a Bucket full of that Liquid in the Filter Slot. \\n\\nYou can place the Smart Fluid Pipe later in the Pipe system to only send that certain Fluid through the Pipes after it. \\n\\nThis is helpful for mass sorting a bunch of Fluid Tanks!]&f"]
	quest.087F6C09CB5B2D1A.title: "&b&a智能流体管道&f&7[Smart Fluid Pipe]&f"
	quest.09936F8FCEA72C5C.quest_desc: [
		"&a&a矿车装配机&f&r可以放置在铁轨上.如果你在其顶部建造任何东西,当&a装配机&r收到&4红石信号&r时,一个&7矿车&r会将其拾取.\\n&7[The Cart Assembler can be placed on tracks. Anything you build on top of it will be picked up by a Minecart if the Assembler has a Redstone signal.]&f"
		""
		"方块必须&a粘合&r在一起,并且任何需要&d旋转动力&r的方块都会自动工作.\\n&7[The Blocks must be Glued together and any Blocks requiring Rotational Power will automatically be working.]&f"
		""
		"要从&7矿车&r上”卸载”方块,只需关闭&4红石信号&r并让&7矿车&r驶过即可.\\n&7[To \"unmount\" the Blocks from the Minecart, simply turn off the Redstone signal and let the Minecart ride through.]&f"
	]
	quest.09936F8FCEA72C5C.title: "&a&a矿车装配机&f&7[Cart Assembler]&f"
	quest.09E34E1F9C751458.quest_desc: ["&d&a竖直十字齿轮箱&f&r就像普通的&d齿轮箱&r被人旋转了一样.\\n\\n它有4个内部的&8传动杆&r,只是这次不是基本方向,而是(从你放置它的位置看)前、后、上、下.\\n\\n也和普通的&d齿轮箱&r一样,它会保持来自原始&8传动杆&r的速度和应力单位!\\n&7[The Vertical Gearbox is just like the normal Gearbox if someone rotated it. \\n\\nIt has 4 internal Shafts just this time instead of the Cardinal Directions, they are (from where you place it) Front, Back, Up, and Down. \\n\\nAlso like the normal Gearbox, it will keep the Speed and Stress Units from the original Shaft!]&f"]
	quest.09E34E1F9C751458.title: "&d&a竖直十字齿轮箱&f&7[Vertical Gearbox]&f"
	quest.0A4962728C98DAD9.quest_desc: ["Item Vaults, while not new, will be used a ton in the new Update! \\n\\nItem Vaults will act like Chests, just we can't put Items in or out as easily as Chests... \\n\\nIn order to move Items we'll need to use Funnels! Attach them to the Vaults to send Items in and out. Preferably Brass Funnels for more Item Filtering. \\n\\nEach Vault has a ton of storage but we can also place them next to each other to combine their Inventories. \\n\\nWe can place them in 1x1, 2x2, or 3x3 and their length can be up to 3 times their width! So the biggest we can have is 3x3x9."]
	quest.0A4962728C98DAD9.title: "&e物品仓库&7[Item Vaults]&f"
	quest.0CF69DBA9573A7B3.quest_desc: [
		"&a蓝图桌&f可以从你的示意图中读取和写入结构.\\n&7[The Schematic Table will read and write structures to/from your schematics.]&f"
		""
		"你可以用它来复制建筑或与他人分享!\\n&7[You can use it to copy buildings or to share them with others!]&f"
	]
	quest.0F16498769DFB3B0.quest_desc: ["我们需要那么多&8安山岩&r做什么？我们需要&8&a安山合金&f&r!\\n\\n&8&a安山合金&f&r由2个&8安山岩&r与2个&7&a铁粒&f&r或2个&7&a锌粒&f&r结合制成.\\n\\n&8&a安山合金&f&r本身用处不大,但它们是几乎所有机器和物品的合成材料.所以,是的,我们需要不少.\\n&7[What will we need all that Andesite for? We'll need Andesite Alloys! \\n\\nAndesite Alloys are made by combining 2 Andesite with either 2 Iron Nuggets or 2 Zinc Nuggets. \\n\\nAndesite Alloys don't do much on their own, rather they are the Crafting Ingredient for almost all Machines and Items. So yeah, we'll need a few.]&f"]
	quest.0F16498769DFB3B0.title: "&8&a安山合金&f&7[Andesite Alloys]&f"
	quest.12274935C3D20C74.quest_desc: ["就像&6&lATM10&r中所有的建造技巧一样,我无法教你如何设计你的&5列车&r……但我可以给些提示!\\n\\n有很多不同的建筑方块可以使用,许多&6&l机械动力&r的外壳看起来很整洁,混凝土可以帮助营造更平滑的外观.\\n\\n你也可以在&5列车&r内部使用门和活板门,这些在&5列车&r移动时也可以使用.\\n\\n如何让它看起来漂亮？楼梯、台阶和活板门有助于塑造形状,飞轮或&d齿轮&r可以提供漂亮的圆边.\\n\\n你甚至可以在上面放个营火来做个&a蒸汽机&f!\\n&7[Like the entirety of Building Tips in lATM10, I can't teach you how to design your Train... but I can give Tips! \\n\\nThere is tons of different Building Blocks you can use, lots of the lCreate Casings look clean and Concretes can help give a more slick look. \\n\\nYou can also use Doors and Trapdoors within the Train which can also be used when the Train is moving. \\n\\nWhat about making it look pretty? Well Stairs, Slabs, and Trapdoors help give Shape to it as well as the Flywheel or Cogs give nice round edges. \\n\\nHeck you can even put a Campfire on it to make a Steam Engine!]&f"]
	quest.12274935C3D20C74.title: "装饰你的&5列车&r&7[Decorating your Train]&f"
	quest.127F9EAC7C305BF5.quest_desc: ["相信我,你会需要一把&6扳手&r!\\n\\n&6扳手&r是&6&l机械动力&r中完美的瑞士军刀式工具.你可以旋转方块、破坏它们、设置它们的配置,有什么是它不能做的!\\n\\n要破坏方块,只需按住潜行键并&a右击&f任何&6&l机械动力&r方块,它就会破坏它们.\\n\\n要旋转方块,只需用&6扳手&r正常&a右击&f它们.不幸的是,这不会给我们免费的&d旋转动力&r,但对于纠正失误仍然有用!\\n\\n它对于设置&a机械装置&r也很有用,但那是后话了.\\n&7[Trust me when I say, you'll need a Wrench! \\n\\nThe Wrench is the perfect Swiss Army Knife like Tool for lCreate. You can rotate Blocks, break them, set their configs, what can't you do with it! \\n\\nTo break Blocks just Shift Right Click any lCreate Block and it'll break them. \\n\\nTo Rotate a Block just normal Right Click them with the Wrench. Unfortunately this doesn't give us free Rotational Power, but it is still useful for slip ups! \\n\\nIt will also be useful for setting up Contraptions, but that is for later.]&f"]
	quest.127F9EAC7C305BF5.title: "&6扳手&7[Wrench]&f"
	quest.133CA315A1443A49.quest_desc: ["&b&a机械泵&f&r将使用旋转动力通过&b管道&r移动&b流体&r.\\n\\n首先,用&b&a机械泵&f&r替换一段&b管道&r.然后,确保它面向你希望&b流体&r被移动的正确方向.内部&6齿轮&r旁边的&a箭头&f会指示移动方向,你可以用扳手改变它.\\n\\n然后,用附近的&6齿轮&r为其提供&d旋转动力&r.方向无关紧要,但速度会影响&b流体&r移动的快慢.\\n\\n&b&a机械泵&f&r也是其他机器(如&b&a软管滑轮&f&r)所需要的!\\n&7[Mechanical Pumps will use Rotational Power to move Fluids through Pipes. \\n\\nFirst, replace a Pipe with the Mechanical Pump. Then, make sure it is facing the right way you want Fluids to be moved. The Arrows next to the internal Cog will tell which direction it will move, you can change that with a Wrench. \\n\\nThen, feed it Rotational Power with a Cog near it. The direction does not change anything, but the Speed will effect how quickly Fluids are moved. \\n\\nMechanical Pumps will also be needed for other Machines like the Hose Pulley!]&f"]
	quest.133CA315A1443A49.title: "&b&a机械泵&f&7[Mechanical Pump]&f"
	quest.13AEBC331F29BC3D.quest_desc: ["&e物品物流&r对&6&l机械动力&r很重要.&6石磨&r需要&e物品&f,&6部署器&f需要&e物品&f,&6&a动力搅拌器&f&f需要&e物品&r,等等.\\n\\n那么&6&l机械动力&r希望我们如何移动&e物品&r呢？用&e传送带&r!\\n\\n&e传送带&r可以连接到两个&8传动杆&r上,随它们一起连接和移动.如果第一个&8传动杆&r&e&o顺时针&r移动,第二个将以相同的速度和方向移动.\\n\\n放置在这些&8传动杆&r上的&e传送带&r也是如此,它们将以与它们之间放置的&8传动杆&r相同的速度和方向移动.\\n\\n放置&8传送带&r时,它们可以完美地水平、垂直或呈45度角对角线放置.\\n\\n一旦放置并移动,任何&e物品&r或实体都会随&e传送带&r移动.不过实体可以走下&e传送带&r,所以要小心.好在&e物品&r在上面时不会走下来,甚至不会消失!\\n\\n然后&e物品&r会被带到&e传送带&r通往的任何地方.如果它突然终止,&e物品&r就会被掉落.如果它通向一个&e存放处&r,&e物品&r就会被放入&e存放处&r.如果它从&6机器&r下方经过,&6机器&r就会使用它.\\n\\n如果你想从&e传送带&r上取下&e物品&f,只需&a右击&f它!\\n&7[Item Logistics is important to lCreate. Millstones need Items, Deployers need Items, Mechanical Mixers need Items, and so on. \\n\\nNow how does lCreate want us to move Items? With Belts! \\n\\nBelts can be attached to two Shafts to connect and move with them. If the first Shaft is moving Clockwise, the second will move same Speed and Direction. \\n\\nSame with the Belts that are placed on those Shafts, they will move same Speed and Direction as the Shafts they are placed between. \\n\\nWith placing Belts they can be placed perfectly Horizontal, Vertical, or diagonal at 45% angles. \\n\\nOnce placed and move, any Items or Entities will be moved with the Belt. Entities can walk off the Belts though so careful with that. Thankfully Items can't walk off or even despawn when on it! \\n\\nThe Items will then be taken to wherever the Belt goes. If it abruptly ends, the Items will just be Dropped. If it goes to a Depot, the Item will be placed in a Depot. If it goes below a Machine, the Machine will use it. \\n\\nIf you want to take Items off the Belt you can just Right Click it!]&f"]
	quest.13AEBC331F29BC3D.title: "&e&l物品物流&7[lItem Logistics]&f"
	quest.16B0C1F7B951C19D.quest_desc: ["现在我们有了&e打包机&r,我们就可以拥有&e包裹&r了!\\n\\n有4种变体,但除了外观外,它们没有任何区别.你得到哪一种完全是随机的.\\n\\n&e包裹&r是&e物品&r,当放置在地面上时会变成实体.放置后你可以&a右击&f它们来拾取,或者破坏它们来取出&e物品&r.你也可以像移动其他实体一样移动它们!\\n\\n&e包裹&r也可以用来与其他&6机器&r交互.比如放置在&8链式传送带&f或&e传送带&r上!\\n&7[Now we have our Packager we can now have Packages! \\n\\nThere is 4 variants but that doesn't change anything with them besides appearance. It is entirely random which one you get. \\n\\nPackages are Items and when Placed on the Ground will become Entities. You can Right Click them after they were Placed to Pick them up, or Break them to get the Items out. You can also move them like any other Entity! \\n\\nPackages can also be used to interact with other Machines. Like being placed on Chain Conveyors or Belts!]&f"]
	quest.16B0C1F7B951C19D.title: "&e纸板包裹&7[Cardboard Packages]&f"
	quest.1712C3B3CF158843.quest_desc: ["要制作&e&a精密构件&f&r,我们需要3个&6部署器&r、3个&e存放处&f/&e传送带&r、1个&e&a金板&f&r、5个齿轮、5个&a大齿轮&f和5个&7&a铁粒&f&r,以及运气!\\n\\n拿出你的&e&a金板&f&r(可以通过压制&a金锭&f制成),并按顺序将其放置在每个部署器的下方.\\n\\n第一个需要一个齿轮,第二个需要一个大齿轮,第三个需要一个&a铁粒&f.\\n\\n然后,当它经过所有3个处理之后,重复这个过程!并且连续做5次.\\n\\n最后,实际上只有80%的几率能成功.另外20%会让你所有的努力都化为乌有!\\n&7[To make the Precision Mechanism we'll need 3 Deployers, 3 Depots/Belts, 1 Gold Plate, 5 Cogs, 5 Large Cogwheels, and 5 Iron Nuggets, as well as luck! \\n\\nTake your Gold Plate (which can be made from Pressing a Gold Ingot) and place it beneath each of the Deployers in order. \\n\\nThe first will need a Cog, the second will need a Large Cog, and the third will need an Iron Nugget. \\n\\nThen, once it has been processed through all 3 of them, repeat it! And do it 5 times in a row. \\n\\nAt the end, there is only an 80% chance it will actually make it. The other 20% will see all your work going POOF!]&f"]
	quest.1712C3B3CF158843.title: "&e&a精密构件&f&7[Precision Mechanism]&f"
	quest.18914FDF9CF9EEA8.quest_desc: ["&a&a发条轴承&f&r在获得&d旋转动力&r时,会根据一天中的时间移动.\\n\\n&a&a发条轴承&f&r前方的方块会自动&a粘合&r到它上面,但其他方块可以&a粘合&r到该方块上以加入移动!\\n\\n如果你想让你的&a时钟&r有更多指针,可以在第一个方块前面添加更多方块,但要确保这些方块没有&a粘合&r在一起.\\n\\n你可以通过手持&a轴承&r来改变哪个指针是哪个,以决定第一个指针(最近的方块)是时针还是分针.\\n&7[Clockwork Bearings will move based on the Time of Day when given Rotational Power. \\n\\nThe Block in front of the Clockwork Bearing will automatically Glue to it, but other Blocks can be Glued to that Block to join it! \\n\\nIf you want more Hands to your Clock, add more Blocks in front of the first Block, but make sure these aren't Glued together. \\n\\nYou can change which Hands are which by Holding on the Bearing to change whether the first Hand (closest Block) is the Hour or Minute Hand. ]&f"]
	quest.18914FDF9CF9EEA8.title: "&a&a发条轴承&f&7[Clockwork Bearing]&f"
	quest.1B182A30604655E2.quest_desc: ["&c烈焰人燃烧器&r制作起来相当容易,你只需要一些&7&a铁板&f&r和一块&4下界岩&r.\\n\\n然后你需要使用&o&a神秘转化&f&r让它不那么空!也就是用你的&c空的烈焰人燃烧器&r&a右击&f一个&c烈焰人&r.\\n\\n然而,当我们放置它时,它看起来有点小而且……温吞吞的……\\n\\n我们需要喂它!不,不是牛排,&c烈焰人&r不喜欢牛排.它需要熔炉燃料,比如木头或煤炭,或者它的最爱:&c&a烈焰蛋糕&f&r!\\n\\n&a熔炉&f燃料只会让它们稍微加热,但&c&a烈焰蛋糕&f&r会让它们&b过热&r!是的,&b过热&r比&6橙色&r热更热.\\n\\n一些配方和&6机器&r需要被加热,比如&6&a自动酿造&f&r、&6搅拌&r和&a蒸汽锅炉&f!\\n&7[Blaze Burners are pretty easy to Craft, you'll just need some Iron Plates with a singular Block of Netherrack. \\n\\nThen you'll need to use a Mysterious Conversion to make it less Empty! That is just Right Clicking a Blaze with your Empty Blaze Burner. \\n\\nWhen we place him though, he seems a little small and... lukewarm... \\n\\nWe'll need to feed him! No, not Steak, Blazes don't like Steaks. He'll need either Furnace Fuels like Wood or Coal, or his favorite: the Blaze Cakes! \\n\\nThe Furnace Fuel will get them only a bit Heated, but the Blaze Cakes will make them Super-Heated! Yes, Super-Heated is hotter than Orange Hot. \\n\\nSome Recipes and Machines will need to be Heated, like Automated Brewing, Mixing, and the Steam Boiler will! ]&f"]
	quest.1B182A30604655E2.title: "&c烈焰人燃烧器&7[Blaze Burner]&f"
	quest.1BA11428DF7541AD.quest_desc: ["因为&e&a可编程齿轮箱&f&r使用了更花哨的&e物品&r,它显然是一台更花哨的&6机器&r!\\n\\n从它那令人困惑的GUI来看,我会这么说……希望我能帮助减少困惑!不过不能保证.\\n\\n像普通的&d换挡齿轮箱&r一样,它需要一个&4&a红石信号&f&r来执行任何设计好的操作.我们需要配置它的GUI来制作一个”脚本”.\\n\\n首先是指令,这些是它将执行的实际任务.在这里,它可以转动它的&8传动杆&r、影响一个滑轮、等待或只是停止.它最终需要停止,这是不可避免的.\\n\\n接下来是角度.&8传动杆&r或滑轮将转动的角度.从360度到1度!\\n\\n最后是速度和方向.它改变传动杆或滑轮移动的速度,以及是&e&o顺时针&r还是&9&o逆时针&r.\\n&7[Because the Sequenced Gearshift uses much fancier Items it is clearly a much fancier Machine! \\n\\nJudging by how confusing its GUI is, I'd say so... Hopefully I can help make it less confusing! No promises though. \\n\\nLike the normal Gearshift it will need a Redstone Signal to do whatever is designed. We'll need to configure its GUI to make a \"script\". \\n\\nFirst, is the Instructions, these are the actual tasks it will preform. Here it can turn its Shaft, effect a Pulley, wait, or just stop. It will need to stop at the end, it is inevitable. \\n\\nNext, is the Angle. The Angle that either the Shaft or Pulley will turn. From 360 to 1 degree! \\n\\nLast is the Speed and Direction. It changes how quickly the Shaft or Pulley move and either Clockwise or Counter-Clockwise.]&f"]
	quest.1BA11428DF7541AD.title: "&e&a可编程齿轮箱&f&7[Sequenced Gearshift]&f"
	quest.1C2309DB4B890E71.quest_desc: ["&b喷口&r与系统一起使用,用于将&b流体&r灌入&e物品&r中.\\n\\n首先,你需要通过&b管道&r将&b流体&r输入&b喷口&r来填充它!\\n\\n然后,如果有一个可以盛装&b流体&r的&e物品&r:桶或玻璃瓶,那么它就会被喷口中的&b流体&r填满.\\n\\n它会自动填充,不需要旋转动力,它利用重力!\\n&7[Spouts are used with systems to fill Items with Fluid. \\n\\nFirst, you'll need to fill the Spout by Piping Fluid into it! \\n\\nThen, if there is a Fluid Holding Item: Bucket or Bottle, then it will be filled with the Fluid in the Spout. \\n\\nIt will automatically fill it, it doesn't need Rotational Power it uses Gravity!]&f"]
	quest.1C2309DB4B890E71.title: "&b喷口&7[Spout]&f"
	quest.1E9B2D814F50A265.quest_desc: ["&6&a鼓风机&f&r是&6&l机械动力&r中最被低估的机器之一.\\n\\n你可以放置它,它会面向你,或者按住潜行键&a右击&f放置让它背对你.\\n\\n当提供&e&o顺时针&r的&d旋转动力&r时,它会吹出空气.当提供&9&o逆时针&r的&d旋转动力&r时,它会吸入空气.\\n\\n这种吸气和吹气也会影响附近的&e物品&r和实体,是的,它旋转得越快,吸气和吹气就越强!\\n\\n我们还可以通过在&6鼓风机&r前面放置一个方块来获得额外的配方.这会影响被&6鼓风机&r吹拂的&e物品&r.\\n\\n我们可以用&c熔岩&r来&6烧炼&e物品&r,就像熔炉一样.从矿石中得到锭,从圆石中得到石头,从工具中得到粒.\\n\\n如果在鼓风机前面放火,我们可以烟熏物品.就像烹饪它们一样!\\n\\n除了熔岩,我们还可以在它前面放水.这会清洗它前面的任何东西,比如把&a混凝土粉末&f变成混凝土.\\n\\n最后,我们可以用&a灵魂火&f代替普通火来附灵物品!这会把物品变成下界变种或完全不同的物品.\\n&7[The Encased Fan is one of the most underrated Machines in lCreate. \\n\\nYou can place it down and it'll face you, or Shift Right Click to place it facing away from you. \\n\\nWhen given Rotational Power Clockwise, it will blow air away from it. When given Rotational Power Counter-Clockwise it will suck air toward it. \\n\\nThese sucks and blows will also effect Items and Entities near them, and yes the faster it spins the more it sucks and blows! \\n\\nWe also get extra Recipes we can make by putting a Block in front of the Fan. This will then effect the Items being blown on by the Fan. \\n\\nWe can use Lava to Blast Items like a Furnace. Getting Ingots from Ores, Stone from Cobble, and Nuggets from Tools. \\n\\nIf we put Fire in front of the Fan we can Smoke Items. Like Cooking them! \\n\\nInstead of Lava we can also place Water in front of it. This will wash whatever is in front of it like Concrete Powder into Concrete. \\n\\nAnd last, instead of Fire we can use Soul Fire to haunt Items! This will change Items either into Nether variants or entirely different Items.]&f"]
	quest.1E9B2D814F50A265.quest_subtitle: "这玩意儿真能吹!&7[This blows!]&f"
	quest.1E9B2D814F50A265.title: "&6&a鼓风机&f&7[Encased Fan]&f"
	quest.24E658BA47367A44.quest_desc: ["&a&a绳索滑轮&f&r会移动连接到其底部&a绳索&r上的任何方块.这也会移动&a粘合&r到那个方块上的任何方块!\\n\\n当被&d旋转动力&r&e&o顺时针&r驱动时,它会降低&a绳索&r,直到碰到另一个方块,或者降到设定的位置.\\n\\n当提供&9&o逆时针&r的&d旋转动力&r时,它会将&a绳索&r拉向&a滑轮&r,直到碰到&a滑轮&r或到达设定的位置.\\n\\n为什么我一直说”设定位置”？因为&a运动模式&f有目的地设置!\\n\\n这些设置将决定方块最终停在哪里!\\n&7[Rope Pulley will move any Blocks that are attached to its Rope at the bottom of it. This will also move any Blocks Glued to that Block! \\n\\nWhen moved Clockwise by Rotational Power, it will lower the Rope until it hits another Block, or to where it is set. \\n\\nWhen given Counter-Clockwise Rotational Power it will move the Rope toward the Pulley until it hits the Pulley or it goes where it is set to go. \\n\\nWhy do I keep saying \"set to go\"? Because there is destination settings with Movement Mode! \\n\\nThese will decide where the Blocks end up stopping!]&f"]
	quest.24E658BA47367A44.title: "&a&a绳索滑轮&f&7[Rope Pulley]&f"
	quest.29917E6196649F5D.quest_desc: ["速度是距离除以时间,也就是从A点移动到B点所需的时间……嗯……我们处理的是&d转速&r,更准确地说,是在这么大的一个圆中,从A点回到A点所需的时间.\\n\\n总之,它决定了我们的&6机械&r移动有多快,包括&d齿轮&r和&8传动杆&r!\\n\\n这很重要,因为速度会影响其他&6机械&r的工作方式.有些需要特定的速度,而另一些在更高速度下工作效率更高.\\n\\n我们可以在动能系统中放置一个转速计(是的,就像汽车里的一样)来查看所有东西的移动速度.\\n&7[Speed is distance over time, AKA how long it takes to get from point A to point B... well... we are working with Revolutions, it is more how long it takes to get from point A to point A in this big of a Circle. \\n\\nAnyways it is how quick our Machines move, including Cogs and Shafts! \\n\\nThis is important because Speed will effect how other Machines work. Some will need a certain Speed and others will work more efficiently at higher Speeds. \\n\\nWe can place a Speedometer (yes, like in a car) into our Kinetic System to see how fast everything is moving.]&f"]
	quest.29917E6196649F5D.title: "速度&7[Speed]&f"
	quest.2AEA51044AD44BE8.quest_desc: ["&e物料库&r可以存放&e物品&r.它们可以存放物品以进行处理,或者将物品存入&e溜槽&r,甚至仅仅用于装饰!\\n\\n你可以在&e传送带&r末端附近放置一个&e溜槽&r,将&e物品&f从&e传送带&f上带到&e物料库&r.\\n\\n&e物料库&r也可以放置在&6机械&r下方,以处理其中的&e物品&r.\\n&7[Depots will hold Items. They can hold them to process the Items, or deposit to a Chute, or even just for decoration! \\n\\nYou can place a Chute near the end of a Belt to bring Items from the Belt onto the Depot. \\n\\nThe Depot can also be placed beneath a Machine to process Items within it. ]&f"]
	quest.2AEA51044AD44BE8.title: "&e物料库&7[Depot]&f"
	quest.2BB3DB19D5EFC7E2.quest_desc: ["&d离合器&r可以连接到我们的动能系统中,其作用类似于一个&a栅栏门&f.\\n\\n给它一个&4&a红石信号&f&r,它将阻止&d旋转动力&r通过.\\n\\n因此,如果&d离合器&r被&4红石&r激活,所有&d旋转&r都会在&d离合器&r处停止.不过,那些&d旋转&r进入它的部分仍会正常&d旋转&r!\\n&7[The Clutch can be connected to our Kinetic Systems where it will act like a Fence Gate. \\n\\nBy giving it a Redstone Signal it will stop the flow of Rotational Power through it. \\n\\nSo all Rotating will stop at the Clutch if it is powered with Redstone. The ones Rotating into it will continue Rotating as normal though!]&f"]
	quest.2BB3DB19D5EFC7E2.title: "&d离合器&7[Clutch]&f"
	quest.2C2958E38293717E.quest_desc: ["要开始制作新的&6&l机械动力&r&e物品&r,我们需要&e纸板&r!\\n\\n它由&6压制&r纸浆制成.\\n\\n纸浆是通过在&6&a动力搅拌器&f&r和&8混合盆&r中&6混合&r4个树苗和&9水&f制成的.\\n\\n你可以组合&e纸板&r来制作&e纸板块&r,这可以用来制作&6&l机械动力&r中的新&e物品&r……或者&e纸板盔甲&r!\\n&7[To start with the new lCreate Items we'll need Cardboard! \\n\\nWhich is made from Pressing Pulp. \\n\\nPulp is made from Mixing 4 Saplings and Water in a Mechanical Mixer and Basin. \\n\\nYou can combine Cardboards to make Blocks of Cardboard which can make the new Items in lCreate... or Cardboard Armor!]&f"]
	quest.2C2958E38293717E.title: "&6&l机械动力&r 1.21&7[lCreate 1.21]&f"
	quest.2D41B04C75FA02BC.quest_desc: ["&6&a动力辊压机&f&r对于制造更多&6机械&r非常有帮助!\\n\\n当提供&d旋转动力&r(以及大量应力单位)时,它会将&6&a金属冲压机&f&r压向它下方的方块.就像一个&a液压机&f!\\n\\n它下方的任何物品:无论是在&e传送带&r上、&e物料库&r上,甚至只是掉落在地,都会被&6压制&r.\\n\\n这主要用于将&7锭&f无损耗地变成&7板&r.你也可以用它从甘蔗获得纸,从泥土获得路径!\\n\\n如果你在它下面放置一个&8混合盆&r,就可以使用&6压制机&r来组合&b流体&r、&e物品&r和方块,以创造新的&e物品&r.\\n\\n在我们的压制机下方使用&8混合盆&r的另一个选项是压实合成.这是针对仅包含一种类型&e物品&r的配方的自动化合成,例如将9个&7&a铁锭&f&f合成一个&7铁块&r.\\n&7[The Mechanical Press is very helpful for making even more Machines! \\n\\nWhen powered with Rotational Power (and a lot of Stress Units) it will send the Metal Press down to Blocks below it. Like a Hydraulic Press! \\n\\nAny Items below it: either on a Belt, Depot, or even just dropped, will be Pressed. \\n\\nThis is mainly for turning Ingots into Plates with no charge. You can also use it to get Paper from Sugarcane and Paths from Dirt! \\n\\nIf you place a Basin beneath it you can then use the Press to combine Liquids, Items, and Blocks to create new Items. \\n\\nAnother option with the Basin below our Press is Compacting Crafting. This is automated Crafting for Recipes that contain only one type of Item, like 9 Iron Ingots into an Iron Block.]&f"]
	quest.2D41B04C75FA02BC.title: "&6&a动力辊压机&f&7[Mechanical Press]&f"
	quest.2D96965317D3CFEC.quest_desc: ["耶,复杂的主题!这次是&5列车长&r和&5列车时刻表&r.\\n\\n首先是获取我们的&5列车长&r,这些可以是任何可用拴绳牵引的生物或&c烈焰人燃烧器&r.如果我们在列车控制装置旁边有一个座位,我们可以将生物用拴绳牵引到座位上,它会等待成为&5列车长&r.\\n\\n&c烈焰人燃烧器&r工作方式类似,只是不需要座位,它们自带座位.\\n\\n然后,我们可以将填写好的&5时刻表&r交给我们的生物或&c烈焰人燃烧器&r,赋予它们该任务,外加一顶&5列车长帽&r.\\n\\n&5时刻表&r是可以”编码”的物品,用于命令我们的&5列车长&r执行特定任务.任务包括:前往&5车站&r、拾取或交付包裹、更改标题或更改最大速度.\\n\\n一旦我们添加了一个任务,就可以编辑其配置,以更改它何时开始下一个任务!这些可以是等待特定时间、一天中的时间、&5列车&r中的物品数量,甚至是&4红石&r信号!\\n&7[Yay, complicated subjects! This time it is Conductors and Train Schedules. \\n\\nFirst is getting our Conductor, these are any Lead-able Mobs or Blaze Burners. If we have a Seat next to the Train Controls we can Lead a Mob into the Seat where it will wait to become a Conductor. \\n\\nBlaze Burners work similar, just without the need for a seat, they bring their own. \\n\\nThen, we can hand our Mob or Blaze Burner, a filled out Schedule to give them that task plus a Conductor's Hat. \\n\\nSchedules are Items that can be \"Coded\" to order our Conductors to preform certain tasks. The tasks are either: go to Station, pickup or drop off Packages, change title, or change max speed. \\n\\nOnce we add a task, we can edit its configs to change when it will start the next task! These can be either a certain Time waited, Time of Day, amount of stuff in Train, or even Redstone!]&f"]
	quest.2D96965317D3CFEC.title: "&5列车长&7[Conductors]&f"
	quest.3029E1E133B91ED8.quest_desc: ["&6&a机械钻头&f&r可以在&a机械装置&r内部或外部使用.外部使用需要&d旋转动力&r,但执行的任务相同.\\n\\n&6&a机械钻头&f&r会挖掘其前方(它能挖掘的)任何方块.\\n\\n它的挖掘速度取决于&d旋转动力&r提供的速度.如果&a机械装置&r连接有容器,挖掘出的方块将被放入其中,而不是掉在地上.\\n\\n是的,&6钻头&r有限制,它只有钻石级别的挖掘等级.所以,无法挖掘&6AllTheModium&r!\\n&7[The Mechanical Drill can be used within a Contraption or without. The without will need Rotational Power but still does the same task. \\n\\nThe Mechanical Drill will Mine any Block in front of it (that it can). \\n\\nIt will Mine as fast as the Rotational Power will give. And if there is an Inventory connected to the Contraption, the Mined Block will be put into it, instead of on the floor. \\n\\nYes, the Drill has a limit, it only has Diamond Tier for Mining. So, no Mining AllTheModium!]&f"]
	quest.3029E1E133B91ED8.title: "&6&a机械钻头&f&7[Mechanical Drill]&f"
	quest.30AC43222FF9B18A.quest_desc: ["&5&a铁道标识&fals&r与&5非玩家列车长&r一起使用.\\n\\n它们的放置方式类似于&5火车站&f和&5观察器&r,但放置方式决定了箭头的位置.\\n\\n&a箭头&f会限制&5列车长&r可以通过其&5列车&r的位置,如果箭头指向相反方向,&5列车&r将无法通过.\\n\\n你可以添加两个指向相反方向的信号,让&5列车长&r在你想要的任何地方通过.\\n\\n使用一堆&5信号&r,我们可以为&7轨道&r交叉路口制作红绿灯.将&5信号&r放置在交叉路口两侧都有箭头的位置.\\n\\n这将使得如果另一列&5列车&r在交叉路口内,&5列车&r就会停止.这可以防止导致&5列车&r脱轨的碰撞.脱轨的&5列车&r需要扳手才能将它们放回&7轨道&r!\\n&7[Train Signals are used with Conductors who aren't Players. \\n\\nThey place just like Train Stations and Observers, but the way they are placed determines the Arrow placement. \\n\\nThe Arrows will restrict where Conductors can pass their Trains, if the Arrow is facing the opposite way, the Train won't pass. \\n\\nYou can add two Signals facing opposite directions to let Conductors pass wherever you want. \\n\\nWith a bunch of Signals we can make Stop Lights for Track intersections. Place the Signals to where there are Arrows on both sides of the intersection. \\n\\nThis will make it so Trains will stop if another Train is in the intersection. That prevents collisions which Derail Trains. Derailed Trains will need a Wrench to put them back on Track!]&f"]
	quest.30AC43222FF9B18A.title: "&5&a铁道标识&fals&7[Train Signals]&f"
	quest.3314FBC4FEAE1D08.quest_desc: ["&6部署器&r是一个非常有趣的用于”戳”的&6机械&r!\\n\\n所谓”戳\\n&7[Deployer is a very fun Machine for poking! \\n\\nBy poking, I mostly mean Item Interactions that we can preform. Place an Item into the Deployer Hand, and then give it Rotational Power. It will then place the Item into the Block on a Depot or Belt below. \\n\\nThis will mimic many actions that we can do, like adding Wax to Copper. \\n\\nYou'll most likely use it for Andesite/Copper/Brass Casings and Polished Rose Quartz.]&f"]
	quest.3314FBC4FEAE1D08.quest_subtitle: "戳&7[Poke]&f"
	quest.3314FBC4FEAE1D08.title: "&6部署器&7[Deployer]&f"
	quest.3697AAF8F281B247.quest_desc: ["这个有点复杂!所以仔细听!\\n首先是建造实际的&b&a蒸汽机&f&r.&b&a流体储罐&f&r将判断其中可以容纳多少&9水&r,并决定&b&a蒸汽机&f&r的等级.\\n\\n然后,简单地将&b&a蒸汽机&f&r连接到&b&a流体储罐&f&r的侧面,它就会变成一个&b&a蒸汽锅炉&f&r.之后,在&b&a蒸汽机&f&r上放置一个&8传动杆&r,以获得我们的&a动力臂&f,它将从中提供&d旋转动力&r.\\n\\n第二是&c&a热源&f&r.我们需要在&b&a流体储罐&f&r下方有一个&c&a热源&f&r来加热&9水&r.有相当多的&c&a热源&f&r:火、营火、熔岩、&a岩浆块&f,但&c烈焰人燃烧器&r是最好的!\\n\\n&c&a热源&f&r越好,应力单位越多!所以给那些&c烈焰人燃烧器&r喂一些&c&a烈焰蛋糕&f&r,你就会火力全开!\\n\\n第三是&9水&r.这是我们&b&a蒸汽机&f&r的燃料,没有&9水&r就没有蒸汽.\\n\\n不过,你如何用&b管道&r输入&9水&r是你的选择,但对于&6&lATM10&r,我推荐一个水槽和&9&lID&r!\\n&7[This one's a doozy! So listen carefully! \\n1st is constructing the actual Steam Engine. The Fluid Tanks will judge how much Water can be held within it and decide the Level the Steam Engine will be at. \\n\\nThen, simply attach the Steam Engine to the side of the Fluid Tanks and it'll become a Steam Boiler. After, place a Shaft on the Steam Engine to get our Mechanical Arm that will give us Rotational Power from it. \\n\\n2nd is a Heat Source. We'll need a Heat Source beneath the Fluid Tanks to heat up the Water. There's quite a few Heat Sources: Fire, Campfire, Lava, Magma Blocks but Blaze Burners are the best! \\n\\nThe better the Heat Source, the more Stress Units! So feed those Blaze Burners some Blaze Cakes and you'll be rocking! \\n\\n3rd is Water. This is the fuel of our Steam Engine, there wouldn't be Steam without Water. \\n\\nHowever you Pipe in Water is your choice, but for lATM10 I recommend a Sink and lID!]&f"]
	quest.3697AAF8F281B247.title: "&b&a蒸汽机&f&7[Steam Engine]&f"
	quest.38CB5044AB3F859B.quest_desc: ["&a&a强力胶&f&r用于将方块粘在一起!以便用&a机械装置&r移动它们.\\n\\n要将方块&a粘合&r在一起,&a右击&f两个不同的方块,它们之间的所有方块都会被&a粘合&r.如果你想&a解除粘合&r,只需用&a强力胶&f&r&a左击&f它们.\\n\\n不过有一些要求,每个方块必须与其他方块相连,且不能是对角线连接.\\n\\n你也可以将其他&a粘合&r的方块与不同的&a粘合&r方块组合.每个方块都能得到&a胶水&r!\\n\\n此外,这会影响最初&a粘合&r方块附近的其他方块.与&a粘合&r方块相邻的方块会随它们一起移动.附着在&a粘合&r方块上的方块也是如此,比如火把或告示牌.\\n&7[Super Glue is used to attach Blocks together! In order to move them with Contraptions. \\n\\nTo Glue Blocks together, Right Click two different Blocks and all between them will be Glued. If you want to Unglue them, just Left Click them with the Super-Glue. \\n\\nThere is some requirements though, each Block must be connected to the other ones and not diagonally. \\n\\nYou can also combine other Glued Blocks to different Glued Blocks. Everyone gets Glue! \\n\\nPlus this will effect other Blocks near the originally Glued one. Blocks adjacent to Glued Blocks will be moved with them. Same with Blocks that are attached to Glued Blocks, like Torches or Signs.]&f"]
	quest.38CB5044AB3F859B.title: "&a强力胶&7[Super-Glue]&f"
	quest.39A7619B4C5592BE.quest_desc: ["&b&a分液池&f&r是我们可以用来从&e物品&r中大量提取&b流体&r的东西!\\n\\n如果瓶子或桶被扔到&b分液池&r顶部:无论是通过传送带、溜槽还是手,&b流体&r都会被排空到&b分液池&r中.\\n\\n现在空了的&e物品&r随后会被推向&b分液池&r的相反方向,而&b流体&r将留在&b分液池&r中等待被&b管道&r抽出.\\n&7[Item Drains are what we can use to mass extract Fluid from Items! \\n\\nIf a Bottle or Bucket is thrown on top of the Drain: either by Belts, Chutes, or Hands, the Fluid will be emptied into the Drain. \\n\\nThe now empty Item will then be pushed off the Drain in the opposite direction, and the Fluid will be sitting in the Drain waiting to be Piped out.]&f"]
	quest.39A7619B4C5592BE.title: "&b&a分液池&f&7[Item Drain]&f"
	quest.3A4C62865C7CC862.quest_desc: ["&b&a流体储罐&f&r可以容纳&b流体&r.就像箱子,不过是装&9水&r之类的!\\n\\n你只能用桶输入&b流体&r,但使用&b管道&r,你可以从它们输入和输出&b流体&r.\\n\\n每个&b&a流体储罐&f&r可以容纳8桶或8000mB的&b流体&r.但当我们组合它们时,这个数字会增加!\\n\\n是的,你没听错!我们可以将多个&b&a流体储罐&f&r彼此相邻放置以连接它们的容器.当它们上下堆叠时,最多可堆叠32个,或者以2x2或3x3的方式堆叠.\\n&7[Fluid Tanks can hold Fluids. Like Chests, but for Water and such! \\n\\nYou can only Input Fluids with Buckets but with Pipes you can Input and Output Fluids from them. \\n\\nEach Fluid Tank can hold 8 Buckets or 8000mB of Fluid. But that number will rise when we combine them! \\n\\nYes, you heard me right! We can place multiple Fluid Tanks next to each other to connect their Inventories. They will stack when placed on top of each other up to 32, or by 2x2 or 3x3.]&f"]
	quest.3A4C62865C7CC862.title: "&b&a流体储罐&f&7[Fluid Tanks]&f"
	quest.3AF2BC9A0E298882.quest_desc: ["有了我们的&8&a安山合金&f&r,我们现在可以制作&8&a安山机壳&f&r.\\n\\n获取一些木头,用斧头剥皮,然后用&8&a安山合金&f&r&a右击&f&a去皮木头&f.\\n\\n这将给我们&8&a安山机壳&f&r!\\n\\n&8&a安山机壳&f&r将是许多、许多、许多&6机械&r所必需的!而且装饰起来也很好看.\\n&7[With our Andesite Alloys we can now make Andesite Casing. \\n\\nGet some Wood, Strip it with an Axe, and then Right Click the Stripped Wood with the Andesite Alloy. \\n\\nThat will give us our Andesite Casing! \\n\\nAndesite Casing will be needed for many, many, many Machines! And looks good for decoration.]&f"]
	quest.3AF2BC9A0E298882.title: "&6&l机械&7[lMachines]&f"
	quest.3B3B38B17CF5D81C.quest_desc: ["&e包裹蛙口&r是可爱且有用的&6机械&r,用于混合&e包裹&f和&8链式传送带&r!\\n\\n首先,手持&e蛙口&r&a右击&f&8链式传送带&r上的&8链&f部分,这将把它设置为&e蛙口&r的目的地.\\n\\n然后,放置后我们可以调整它的GUI.在这里,我们可以更改其地址的名称,确定它是接收并给出&e包裹&r还是只给出&e包裹&r.\\n\\n它们有18个槽位来存放&e包裹&r以便移动.\\n\\n如果&e包裹&r的地址与你给&e蛙口&f的地址不匹配,&e蛙口&r会将&e包裹&r发送到&8链式传送带&r上.\\n\\n如果地址匹配,&e包裹&r将被取入&e蛙口&r.如果没有匹配的地址,&e包裹&r就会一直转圈!\\n\\n&e包裹&r也可以通过&e漏斗&f和&e传送带&r自动从&e蛙口&r发送和取出.\\n&7[Package Frogports are adorable and helpful Machines used for mixing Packages and Chain Conveyors! \\n\\nFirst, Right Click a part of the Chain on a Chain Conveyor with the Frogport in Hand, this will set it as the Frogports destination. \\n\\nThen, when placed we can mess with its GUI. Here we can change the name of its Address, determine whether it takes and gives Packages or just gives Packages. \\n\\nThey have 18 Slots to Hold Packages for moving. \\n\\nIf the Address of the Package doesn't match the Address you gave the Frogport, the Frogport will send the Package onto the Chain Conveyor. \\n\\nIf it matches the Address, the Package will be taken into the Frogport. If there is no matching Address the Package will just go in circles! \\n\\nPackages can also be automatically sent and taken from Frogports with Funnels and Belts.]&f"]
	quest.3B3B38B17CF5D81C.title: "&e包裹蛙口&7[Package Frogport]&f"
	quest.3C892B33758B7BA6.quest_desc: ["&d齿轮&f和&d大型齿轮&r可以相互作用以改变速度和应力!\\n\\n如果你将一个&d齿轮&r与一个&d大型齿轮&r对角线连接,&d齿轮&r的速度将加倍!这是因为&d大型齿轮&r比&d齿轮&r有更多的齿,完成一次完整的&d旋转&r需要更长的时间.\\n\\n反之亦然,如果你将一个&d大型齿轮&r与一个&d齿轮&r对角线放置,&d大型齿轮&r将以一半的速度旋转.\\n\\n这些也会改变来自&d齿轮&r的应力单位.速度越快,应力越大.速度越慢,应力越小.\\n&7[Cogs and Large Cogs can interact with each other to change Speed and Stress! \\n\\nIf you connect a Cog, diagonally from a Large Cog, the Cog will double in Speed! This is because the Large Cog has more Teeth than the Cog, it takes longer to take a full Rotation. \\n\\nThis also works in the reverse, if you put a Large Cog diagonal to a Cog, the Large Cog will spin at half Speed. \\n\\nThese will also change the Stress Units from the Cogs. More Speed, more Stress. Less Speed, less Stress.]&f"]
	quest.3C892B33758B7BA6.title: "&d齿轮&r团队合作!&7[Cog Teamwork!]&f"
	quest.3C99017FD32B6DE2.quest_desc: ["&e&a黄铜机壳&f&r的制作方式与&8安山合金&r和&c&a铜机壳&f&r相同.只需将&e物品&r应用到&a去皮木头&f上.\\n\\n但是&e&a黄铜机壳&f&r能给我们带来一些最强大的&6机器&r,所以它不会像&8安山合金&r或&c铜&r那么容易获得.\\n\\n好在这是&6&lATM10&r,所以你可以用很多不同的方法制作&e黄铜&r!\\n\\n但&6&l机械动力&r的方法是,将一个&c&a铜锭&f&r和一个&7&a锌锭&f&r扔进&6&a动力搅拌器&f&r下面的&8盆&r里,同时&8盆&r被加热.\\n&7[Brass Casings are made the same way as Andesite and Copper Casings. Just apply the Item to Stripped Wood. \\n\\nBut with Brass Casings giving us some of the most powerful Machines, it won't be as easy to get as Andesite or Copper. \\n\\nThankfully this is lATM10 so you can make Brass in many different ways! \\n\\nBut the lCreate way would be to throw a Copper Ingot and Zinc Ingot into a Basin below a Mechanical Mixer, while the Basin is heated.]&f"]
	quest.3C99017FD32B6DE2.title: "&e&a黄铜机壳&f&7[Brass Casing]&f"
	quest.3D2A03EB2B91E9C1.quest_desc: ["这些基本上就是花哨的漏斗.\\n\\n它们连接两个容器,将&e物品&r从上面的容器带到下面的容器.\\n\\n&e溜槽&r可以相互连接,甚至是对角连接.\\n\\n你还可以将它们与&6鼓风机&r一起使用,将&e物品&r沿着&e溜槽&r向上吹!\\n&7[These are literally just fancy Hoppers. \\n\\nThey connect two Inventories, bringing Items from the Top one to the Bottom one. \\n\\nChutes can connect to each other, even diagonally. \\n\\nYou can also use them with Fans to shoot Items up the Chutes!]&f"]
	quest.3D2A03EB2B91E9C1.title: "&e溜槽&7[Chute]&f"
	quest.3F02EF19112D23BE.quest_desc: ["你需要&6机械合成器&r来制作&6&a粉碎轮&f&r,它们对于3x3的工作台来说太大了.你还需要大量的&8&a安山合金&f&r.\\n\\n顺便说一句,你实际上需要2个才能使用它们.\\n一旦你有了2个,把它们并排放置.然后,给它们都提供&d旋转动力&r和大量的应力单位.\\n\\n确保&6&a粉碎轮&f&r以相反的方向旋转,否则它不会&6粉碎&r!左边的必须&e&o顺时针&r旋转,右边的必须&9&o逆时针&r旋转.\\n\\n一旦它们开始旋转(快速且方向正确),你可以让&e物品&r掉落在它们之间,它们就会被&6粉碎&r.\\n\\n什么&e物品&r？从矿石中得到&6粉碎&r矿石,从石头和下界岩中得到&e物品&r,从沙砾中得到沙子和燧石,甚至从下界疣块中得到下界疣!\\n&7[You'll need Mechanical Crafters to make the Crushing Wheels, they are too big for a 3x3 Crafting Table. You'll also need a ton of Andesite Alloys. \\n\\nBTW, you'll need 2 to actually use them. \\nOnce you have 2, place them next to each other. Then, feed them both Rotational Power and a lot of Stress Units. \\n\\nMake sure that the Crushing Wheels are spinning in opposite directions or else it won't Crush! The left one must be spinning Clockwise, and the right one must spin Counter-Clockwise. \\n\\nOnce they are spinning (fast and in the right directions) you can have Items Dropped in between them and they will be Crushed. \\n\\nWhat Items? Crushed Ores from Ores, Items from Stones and Netherrack, Sand and Flint from Gravel, and even Netherwart from Netherwart Blocks!]&f"]
	quest.3F02EF19112D23BE.title: "&6&a粉碎轮&f&7[Crushing Wheels]&f"
	quest.3F2C1A81C17D2D67.quest_desc: ["&6&a动力臂&f&r 在放置前必须进行配置,就像 &e&a弹射置物台&f&r 一样.\\n\\n它的作用范围为 4 格,可以从 &e传送带&f 和 &e物流仓库&r 拾取物品.它也可以将物品存入 &e传送带&f、&e物流仓库&f 和 &e漏斗&r.\\n手持 &6&a动力臂&f&r 时,&a右击&f 方块将其设为输入点,再次点击可将其更改为输出点.你可以 &a左击&f 来取消选择方块.你可以选择作用范围内的任意多个方块!\\n\\n一旦它获得 &d旋转动力&r,任何输入方块中有 &e物品&r,且任何输出方块中有空间,它就会开始移动 &e物品&r.给予它的速度越快,它移动得就越快.\\n\\n就像 &e&a黄铜隧道&f&r 一样,&6&a动力臂&f&r 也有分配模式.谢天谢地,模式少多了!&a轮询&f:将按顺序处理输入和输出.&a强制轮询调度&f:将等待直到每个输出都有空间或每个输入都有可用的 &e物品&r.&a第一目标优先&f:将优先处理离它最近的方块.\\n&7[Mechanical Arms must be configured before Placing them, like the Weighted Ejector. \\n\\nIt has a 4 Block Range and can pick up from Belts and Depots. It can also deposit into Belts, Depots, and Funnels. \\nWhile Holding the Mechanical Arm, Right Click Blocks to set as Input, then Click again to change it to Output. You can Left Click to deselect the Blocks. You can select as many are in range! \\n\\nOnce it has Rotational Power, an Item in any Input Block, and space in any Output Block, it will start moving Items. It will go faster the more Speed is given to it. \\n\\nLike the Brass Tunnel, the Mechanical Arm has Distribution Modes. Thankfully a lot less! Round Robin: will go in order for Inputs and Outputs. Forced Round Robin: will wait until every Output has space or every Input has Items available. Prefer First Target: will go for the closest Block to it.]&f"]
	quest.3F2C1A81C17D2D67.quest_subtitle: "既然机器人能做得更好,何必亲自动手？&7[Why do it yourself when Robot can do it better?]&f"
	quest.3F2C1A81C17D2D67.title: "&6&a动力臂&f&7[Mechanical Arm]&f"
	quest.3F663416E824720C.quest_desc: ["&c&a铜机壳&f&r 将是大多数涉及 &b&a流体物流&f&r 的机器所必需的.\\n\\n你想放置 &9水&r？你需要 &c&a铜机壳&f&r.你想拾取 &9水&r？你需要 &c&a铜机壳&f&r.\\n\\n它们的制作方法与 &8&a安山机壳&f&r 类似,将 &c&a铜锭&f&r 应用到去皮原木上即可.\\n&7[Copper Casings will be needed for most Machines involved in Fluid Logistics. \\n\\nYou wanna place Water? You'll need Copper Casings. You wanna pick up Water? You'll need Copper Casings. \\n\\nThey are made just like Andesite Casings, apply a Copper Ingot to a Stripped Log.]&f"]
	quest.3F663416E824720C.title: "&c&a铜机壳&f&7[Copper Casings]&f"
	quest.3FBCBBEBB78B83FC.quest_desc: ["终于可以造 &5火车&r 了!\\n\\n我们应该已经从 &5火车站&r 任务中获得了 &5转向架&r,不,&5转向架&r 的设计并不重要.\\n\\n然后,我们可以用 &a超级胶水&f&r 将方块放置到 &5转向架&r 上.用什么方块都行,几乎所有能被移动的方块都可以被 &a粘合&r!\\n\\n这时候你就可以尝试让它看起来更漂亮!去 Discord 的 Artwork-Builds Showoff 频道看看一些例子.\\n\\n我们的 &5火车&r 最重要的方块是 &5火车控制器&r.你需要一个才能让 &5火车&r 真正动起来.\\n\\n你还可以为 &5列车长&r(稍后详述)甚至你自己添加一个 &5座位&r!\\n\\n一切准备就绪后,只需点击”组装火车\\n&7[Finally make a Train! \\n\\nWe should have our Boogeys from the Train Station Quest, no the design of Boogey doesn't matter. \\n\\nThen, we can place Blocks onto the Boogey with Super-Glue. It doesn't matter what Blocks, pretty much any Block that can be moved can be Glued! \\n\\nThis is when you try and make it look pretty! Check out Artwork-Builds Showoff in Discord to see a few of them. \\n\\nThe most important Block for our Train is the Train Controls. You'll need one in order to actually move the Train. \\n\\nYou can also add a Seat for Conductors (more on that later) or even yourself! \\n\\nOnce it is all ready, just hit \"Assemble Train\" and either your Train will be made, or it will tell you what you did wrong!]&f"]
	quest.3FBCBBEBB78B83FC.title: "建造 &5火车&r&7[Constructing Trains]&f"
	quest.4194397DFD0199C2.quest_desc: ["&6机械合成器&r 可用于 &6自动合成&r 以及比 3x3 合成网格更大的配方,例如 &6&a粉碎轮&f&r.\\n\\n按所需顺序放置 &6机械合成器&r,然后你需要设置配方中 &e物品&r 的流动方向.\\n\\n方向由 &6合成器&r 边缘的箭头指示.这些箭头可以通过用 &6扳手&r &a右击&f 它们来改变!\\n\\n然后,只需用手或通过 &e漏斗&r 自动化地将 &e物品&r 放入 &6机械合成器&r.\\n\\n之后,你可以向任何一个 &6机械合成器&r 提供 &d旋转动力&r(它们共享 &d齿轮&r)来启动配方.\\n\\n如果它不工作,请检查确保每个 &e物品&r 都已放入,每个箭头都指向正确的方向,并且它有足够的 &d旋转动力&r.\\n&7[Mechanical Crafters can be used for Auto-Crafting and Recipes that are bigger than 3x3 Crafting Grid like the Crushing Wheel. \\n\\nPlace the Mechanical Crafters in the order that is needed, then you'll need to set which direction the Items in the recipe go. \\n\\nThe direction is known by the arrows on the edge of the Crafters. These can be changed by Right Clicking them with a Wrench! \\n\\nThen, just place Items into the Mechanical Crafters either with your Hands or automated with Funnels. \\n\\nAfter that, you can supply Rotational Power to any of the Mechanical Crafters (they share Cogs) to start up the Recipes. \\n\\nIf it isn't working, check to make sure every Item is in, every arrow is facing the right way, and it has enough Rotational Power.]&f"]
	quest.4194397DFD0199C2.title: "&6机械合成器&r&7[Mechanical Crafter]&f"
	quest.4285510271B5223D.quest_desc: ["&d齿轮箱&r 有助于将 &d旋转动力&r 传送到许多不同的方向!\\n\\n&a普通&f &d齿轮箱&r 内部有 4 个 &8传动杆&r,分别位于四个基本方向:北、东、南、西.\\n\\n其他 &8传动杆&r 将匹配速度和应力单位,但它们也会以与原始 &8传动杆&r 不同的方向旋转.\\n&7[The Gearbox is helpful for sending Rotational Power in a whole bunch of different directions! \\n\\nThe normal Gearbox will have 4 internal Shafts, on each of the Cardinal Directions: North, East, South, and West. \\n\\nThe other Shafts will match the Speed and Stress Units but they will also spin in different directions from the original Shaft.]&f"]
	quest.4285510271B5223D.title: "&d齿轮箱&r&7[Gearbox]&f"
	quest.459BA85E48B343AE.quest_desc: ["&a径向底盘&r 在连接到其他 &a径向底盘&r 方面与 &a线性底盘&r 类似,但其他方面都不同.\\n\\n你可以在其他 &a径向底盘&r 的顶部或底部连接其他 &a径向底盘&r,它们会自动连接.\\n\\n然后,将 &a胶水&r 涂在 &a径向底盘&r 的侧面,以 &a粘合&r 该 &a底盘&r 设定半径内的所有方块.顺便说一下,半径指的是圆形范围!\\n\\n你可以用 &6扳手&r 右击 &a径向底盘&r 来改变圆形范围的大小.\\n&7[Radial Chasis work similar to Linear Chasis in connecting to other Radial Chasis but everything else changes. \\n\\nYou can connect other Radial Chasis on the top or bottom of other ones and they will automatically connect. \\n\\nThen, Glue the sides of the Radial Chasis to Glue every Block within a set Radius of the Chasis. BTW Radius means circle! \\n\\nYou can change how far the circle goes with a Wrench to the Radial Chasis.]&f"]
	quest.459BA85E48B343AE.title: "&a径向底盘&r&7[Radial Chasis]&f"
	quest.45EC31812FB9934D.quest_desc: ["&a&a动力活塞&f&r 在移动方块方面表现得像普通活塞,但除此之外就没有相似之处了!\\n\\n它们不依赖 &4红石&r 工作,而是使用 &d旋转动力&r.&d旋转动力&r 将决定活塞移动的速度和方向.\\n\\n它们还可以添加 &a&a粘液球&f&r 来 &a粘附&r 到方块上.并且那些方块可以被 &a粘合&r,使所有东西都随活塞一起移动.\\n\\n最棒的是,我们可以在 &a活塞&r 的背面添加 &a&a活塞延长杆&f&r 来改变 &a活塞&r 可以移动的距离!\\n\\n每增加一根新的 &a延长杆&r 就增加 &a1 格&f 距离.我不确定最多能加多少根,也许你可以自己探索一下!\\n&7[Mechanical Pistons act like normal Pistons with Moving Blocks, but after that the similarities end! \\n\\nThey don't work off Redstone, instead they use Rotational Power. The Rotational Power will determine how fast and the direction the Piston moves. \\n\\nThey also can have Slime Balls added to Stick to Blocks. And those Blocks can be Glued to have everything moving with the Piston. \\n\\nBest part is that we can add Piston Extension Poles to the back of the Piston to change how far the Piston can move! \\n\\nEach new Pole adds a new Block of distance. I'm not sure of the max you can add, maybe that is something you can find out yourself!]&f"]
	quest.45EC31812FB9934D.title: "&a&a动力活塞&f&7[Mechanical Pistons]&f"
	quest.476C7317510198D9.quest_desc: ["好吧,这个很有趣!你喜欢扔 &e物品&r 吗？我是说,真的把它们扔出去!\\n\\n那么,&e&a弹射置物台&f&r 就是为你准备的!\\n\\n首先,你需要按住潜行键 &a右击&f 一个方块来将其设为 &e&a弹射置物台&f&r 的目标.目标必须与 &e弹射器&r 瞄准的方向在一条直线上才能命中.\\n\\n一旦它有了目标并被放置下来,就可以给它提供 &d旋转动力&r 来充能!然后,当有 &e物品&r 被放在 &e&a弹射置物台&f&r 上时,它就会将其抛出!\\n你可以按住某些侧面来改变抛出 &e物品&r 所需的堆叠数量.\\n&7[Okay this ones fun! You like throwing Items? Like, I mean to really throw them! \\n\\nThen, the Weighted Ejector is for you! \\n\\nFirst, you need to Shift Right Click a Block with the Weighted Ejector to set it as the target. The target has to be in line with where the Ejector is aimed in order to hit it. \\n\\nOnce it has a target and is placed down, it can be fed Rotational Power to charge it! Then, when an Item is placed on the Weighted Ejector, it will throw it! \\nYou can hold on some of the Sides to change the Stack Size needed to throw Items.]&f"]
	quest.476C7317510198D9.title: "&e&a弹射置物台&f&7[Weighted Ejector]&f"
	quest.47897D827C50629D.quest_desc: ["&a&a活塞延长杆&f&r 是我们制造和扩展 &a&a动力活塞&f&r 的方式.\\n\\n抱歉,不是普通活塞!\\n&7[Piston Extension Poles are how we can make and expand Mechanical Pistons. \\n\\nNot normal Pistons, sorry!]&f"]
	quest.47897D827C50629D.quest_subtitle: "为何只移动这么远？&7[Why only move so far?]&f"
	quest.47897D827C50629D.title: "&a活塞延长杆&r&7[Piston Extension]&f"
	quest.47A6769B6BF1A46D.quest_desc: ["&e漏斗&r 就像是漏斗和发射器生下的孩子.\\n\\n当放置在有容器的方块上时,比如箱子,它会自动一次取出 1 个 &e物品&r.\\n如果你按住潜行键 &a右击&f,它会自动将 &e物品&r 放入容器.\\n\\n两者都可以用 &4&a红石信号&f&r 关闭!\\n&7[Funnels are like if a Hopper and Dispenser had a baby. \\n\\nWhen placed onto a Block with an Inventory, like Chests, it will automatically take Items out 1 at a time. \\nIf you Shift Right Click it will automatically take Items into the Inventory. \\n\\nBoth can be turned off with a Redstone Signal!]&f"]
	quest.47A6769B6BF1A46D.title: "&e&a安山岩漏斗&f&7[Andesite Funnel]&f"
	quest.483892F0A0F75B97.quest_desc: ["&b&a流体传输管道&f&r 是我们用来真正自动将 &b流体&r 从一个容器移动到另一个容器的东西!\\n\\n你可以放置它们,它们会自动连接到容器和其他 &b管道&r.\\n\\n用扳手可以给 &b管道&r 添加窗口.没有窗口的平行 &b管道&r 不会相互连接.\\n\\n不过 &b管道&r 本身不会移动 &b流体&r,我们需要 &b&a机械泵&f&r 来做这件事!\\n\\n当我们确实让 &b管道&r 开始流动时,我们可以用它们从源方块中取出 &b流体&r,或者反过来放置源方块.\\n\\n不过 &b管道&r 需要一个开放的末端才能这样做,所以不能有方块挡路.\\n&7[Fluid Pipes are what we'll use to actually move Fluids automatically from one Inventory to another! \\n\\nYou can place them down and they will automatically connect to Inventories and other Pipes. \\n\\nWith a Wrench you can add Windows to a Pipe. These won't connect to parallel Pipes without Windows. \\n\\nThe Pipes themselves won't move Fluids though, we'll need a Mechanical Pump for that! \\n\\nWhen we do get Pipes to start flowing though, we can use them to take Fluids out from a Source Block or the opposite with placing down Source Blocks. \\n\\nThe Pipe will need to have an Open End to do so though, so there can't be Blocks in the way.]&f"]
	quest.483892F0A0F75B97.title: "&b&a流体传输管道&f&7[Fluid Pipe]&f"
	quest.48BE7DAC5082044D.quest_desc: ["应力,就像 &d旋转动力&r 一样,重要且令人困惑.\\n\\n应力单位(Su)是我们 &6机器&r 的功率负载.有些 &6机器&r 有最小应力,这意味着你的系统中需要有那么多应力才能使该 &6机器&r 工作.\\n\\n&6部署器&f、&6&a动力锯&f&f 和 &6&a鼓风机&f&r 就是例子!\\n\\n有些 &6机器&r 也有最大应力单位.这意味着如果超过这个量,它很可能会停止工作.或者爆炸,两者都有可能!\\n\\n应力单位由 &d齿轮&r 和我们产生 &d旋转动力&r 的 &6机器&r 产生.&9&a水车&f&r 产生的应力很小,而 &d&a蒸汽机&f&r 可以产生大量应力!\\n&7[Stress, like Rotational Power, is important and confusing. \\n\\nStress Units (Su) are power loads for our Machines. Some Machines will have a minimum Stress, that means you'll need that much Stress in your System to work the Machine. \\n\\nDeployers, Mechanical Saws, and Encased Fans are examples of those! \\n\\nSome Machines also have a maximum Stress Units. That means if it goes over the amount, it will most likely stop working. Or blow up, either or! \\n\\nStress Units are developed from Cogs and from our Machines that make Rotational Power. Water Wheels give little Stress while Steam Engines can give a ton!]&f"]
	quest.48BE7DAC5082044D.title: "应力&r&7[Stress]&f"
	quest.495B0CC178B4CFA9.quest_desc: ["&e&a黄铜漏斗&f&r 的放置和使用方式与 &e&a安山岩漏斗&f&r 类似.\\n\\n但每一面都有新的配置选项!\\n\\n输入面现在带有过滤器选项.只需放入 &e物品&r,它就只会接收那种 &e物品&r.\\n\\n输出面现在带有数量限制.你可以滚动设置从 1 到 64 的数字.你还可以选择是精确输出那个数量,还是最多输出那个数量.\\n\\n如果是精确数量,它会等待直到容器内有那个数量的物品才输出.如果是最多数量,它会持续输出 &e物品&r 直到达到那个数字.\\n&7[The Brass Funnel is placed and used similar to the Andesite Funnel. \\n\\nBut each side comes with new configs! \\n\\nThe Input Side will now come with a Filter option. Just place the Item in, and it will only take in that Item. \\n\\nThe Output Side will now come with a limit. You can Scroll to set a number from 1 to 64. You can also choose whether it will Output exactly that amount, or up to that amount. \\n\\nIf it is exactly that amount, it will wait until that amount is within the Inventory to Output it. If it is up to, it will keep Outputting Items until that number is reached.]&f"]
	quest.495B0CC178B4CFA9.title: "&e&a黄铜漏斗&f&7[Brass Funnel]&f"
	quest.4C31649D721F76B5.quest_desc: ["&6&a动力收割机&f&r 会自动收割成熟的作物,并重新种植.\\n\\n显然,它必须由 &a机械装置&r 移动才能工作.\\n\\n它还会自动将收集到的作物放入连接到 &a机械装置&r 的容器中.如果没有,作物会掉落在地上.\\n&7[The Mechanical Harvester will automatically Farm Mature Crops, and Replant them. \\n\\nObviously it has to be moved by a Contraption to work. \\n\\nIt will also automatically place the collected Crops into Inventories connected to the Contraption. If not, it will drop the Crops on the ground.]&f"]
	quest.4C31649D721F76B5.title: "&6&a动力收割机&f&7[Mechanical Harvester]&f"
	quest.4C77ABCD41383F32.quest_desc: ["&c&a烈焰蛋糕&f&r 可以用来 &b超级加热&r &c烈焰燃烧器&r!这是一种前所未见的热度!\\n\\n但我们如何烘烤它们呢？\\n\\n首先,我们需要制作 &4&a烈焰蛋糕胚&f&r.要得到它,需要在 &a动力辊压机&f 和混合盆中处理鸡蛋、糖和 &4&a余烬面粉&f&r.\\n\\n&4&a余烬面粉&f&r 是通过两个 &a粉碎轮&f 粉碎 &4下界岩&r 制成的.\\n\\n然后,一旦我们有了 &4&a烈焰蛋糕胚&f&r,就可以用 &b浇注口&r 的 &c熔岩&r 填充它,制成我们的 &c&a烈焰蛋糕&f&r!\\n&7[Blaze Cakes can be used to Super-Heat Blaze Burners! A Heat that has never been seen before! \\n\\nBut how do we Bake them? \\n\\nFirst, we'll need to make the Blaze Cake Base. To get it, process an Egg, Sugar, and Cinder Flour in a Mechanical Press and Basin. \\n\\nCinder Flour is created by Crushing Netherrack through two Crushing Wheels. \\n\\nThen, once we have our Blaze Cake Base, we can fill it with Lava from a Spout to make our Blaze Cake!]&f"]
	quest.4C77ABCD41383F32.title: "&c&a烈焰蛋糕&f&7[Blaze Cakes]&f"
	quest.4EE10B8E194F5CA9.quest_desc: ["&6&l机械动力&r 1.21 版本现在也在基础模组中包含了火车.\\n\\n首先,你需要 &5坚固金属&r!\\n\\n粉碎 &5黑曜石&r 得到 &5&a黑曜石粉&f&r.然后,使用 &b浇注口&r 将 &c熔岩&r 注入 &5&a碎黑曜石&f&r.\\n\\n之后,用 &6&a动力辊压机&f&r 压制两次,你就会得到 &5坚固金属&r.\\n\\n&5坚固金属&r 然后可以应用到 &e&a黄铜机壳&f&r 上,制成 &5火车外壳&r.\\n&7[lCreate 1.21 also now comes with Trains included with the base Mod. \\n\\nFirst, you'll need Sturdy Metal! \\n\\nCrush Obsidian to get Obsidian Dust. Then, use a Spout to place Lava into the Crushed Obsidian. \\n\\nAfter that, Press it twice with Mechanical Presses and you'll get Sturdy Metal. \\n\\nSturdy Metal can then be applied to a Brass Casing to make Train Casings.]&f"]
	quest.4EE10B8E194F5CA9.title: "&5&l火车&r&7[lTrains]&f"
	quest.50DBB87E53017E60.quest_desc: ["&b&a流体阀&f&r 可以用来阻止 &b管道&r 移动 &b流体&r.\\n\\n给它们一个旋转(很可能来自 &c阀门手柄&r),以停止移动 &b流体&r.\\n\\n只需再次旋转它,&b流体&r 就会恢复流动!\\n&7[Fluid Valves can be used to stop Pipes from moving Fluid. \\n\\nGive them a Rotation, most likely from a Valve Handle, to stop moving Fluids. \\n\\nJust Rotate it again to get the Fluids back!]&f"]
	quest.50DBB87E53017E60.title: "&b&a流体阀&f&7[Fluid Valve]&f"
	quest.5134C81D96C55375.quest_desc: ["&5火车观察器&r 的工作原理类似于一个高级的探测铁轨.\\n\\n当 &5火车&r 驶过它所设置的 &7轨道&r(像 &5火车站&r 一样选择)时,它会发出一个 &4&a红石信号&f&r.\\n\\n你还可以在 &5观察器&r 中放置过滤器,只有当 &5火车&r 内部有那种 &e物品&r 或 &b流体&r 时才会发出 &4&a红石信号&f&r.\\n&7[Train Observers work like a fancy Detection Rail. \\n\\nWhen a Train rolls over it the Track it is set to (which is chosen like the Train Station) it will give a Redstone Signal. \\n\\nYou can also place Filters into the Observer to only get Redstone Signals when the Train has that Item or Fluid within.]&f"]
	quest.5134C81D96C55375.title: "&5火车观察器&r&7[Train Observer]&f"
	quest.51EA6B1452883AB2.quest_desc: ["线性底盘的工作原理就像现实生活中的橡皮泥,只相互连接.\\n\\n朝向相同的线性底盘会自动连接,就像被粘合了一样.其他线性底盘或朝向不同的底盘不会粘在一起.\\n\\n然后你可以在线性底盘的顶部和底部使用胶水,从它开始连接一列方块.所以那些方块上面的所有方块都会被粘合到线性底盘上.对于节省胶水非常有帮助!\\n\\n用扳手可以设置在线性底盘顶部或底部粘合多少个方块.\\n&7[Linear Chasis work like Puddy in real life, only connecting to each other. \\n\\nLinear Chasis, which are facing the same way, will automatically connect as if they were Glued. Other Linear Chasis or ones facing different ways, will not stick together. \\n\\nYou can then use Glue on the Top and Bottom of the Linear Chasis to connect a line of Blocks from it. So all Blocks on top of those will be Glued to the Linear Chasis. Very helpful for saving Glue! \\n\\nWith the Wrench you can set how many Blocks get Glued on the Top or Bottom of the Linear Chasis.]&f"]
	quest.51EA6B1452883AB2.title: "&a线性底盘&r&7[Linear Chasis]&f"
	quest.54EC1C7FC1DA9107.quest_desc: ["&d可调链式传动箱&r的工作原理类似于&d&a链式传动箱&f&r,只是有更多配置.\\n\\n如果我们向原始&8传动杆&r连接的&d可调链式传动箱&r发送一个&4&a红石信号&f&r,其他&d链式传动箱&r的&8传动杆&r速度将加倍!\\n\\n但是,如果我们向另一个不同的&d链式传动箱&r发送信号,那个&d链式传动箱&r的速度将减半!\\n&7[Adjustable Chain Drives work like Encased Chain Drives, just with more configs. \\n\\nIf we send a Redstone Signal to the Adjustable Chain Drive that the original Shaft is connected to, the other Chain Drive Shafts will double in Speed! \\n\\nIf we send one to a different Chain Drive though, the Speed of that Chain Drive will be cut in half!]&f"]
	quest.54EC1C7FC1DA9107.title: "&d可调链式传动箱&7[Adjustable Chain Drive]&f"
	quest.57A18F2E51952EB8.quest_desc: ["&5邮箱&r将使用地址和&5火车&r来递送&e包裹&r!\\n\\n首先,&e包裹&r可以通过&e仓库&r存放在&5火车&r上!显然,&e仓库&r需要通过&a粘液球&r连接到&5火车&r.\\n\\n接下来,我们可以通过手持&5邮箱&r&a右击&f&5火车站&r来将&5邮箱&r分配给&5火车站&r.\\n\\n然后我们可以将&5邮箱&r放置在附近,当&5火车&r到达&5车站&r时,它们会与&5邮箱&r交互.\\n\\n在&5邮箱&r的GUI中,我们可以更改其地址,这将影响&e包裹&r是递送到这里还是从这里发送.如果&e包裹&r的地址与&5邮箱&r的地址匹配,它将被发送到&5邮箱&r.如果不匹配,它将从&5邮箱&r发送到你的&5火车&r上!\\n&7[Postboxes will use Addresses and Trains to deliver Packages! \\n\\nFirst, Packages can be held on Trains with Depots! Obviously the Depot needs to be connected to the Train via Glue. \\n\\nNext, we can assign the Postbox to a Train Station by Right Clicking the Train Station with the Postbox in Hand. \\n\\nWe can then place the Postbox nearby and when a Train arrives at the Station they will interact with the Postbox. \\n\\nIn the Postbox's GUI we can change its Address, which will effect whether Packages are delivered or sent from it. If the Address of the Package matches the Address of the Postbox, it will be sent to the Postbox. If it doesn't match, it will go from the Postbox to your Train!]&f"]
	quest.57A18F2E51952EB8.title: "&5邮箱&7[Postboxes]&f"
	quest.57A7A5C79389A96A.quest_desc: ["大多数玩家应该已经知道&6&l机械动力&r,尤其是它那数不清的附属模组!没有多少模组有围绕它们构建的整个整合包!\\n\\n如果你不熟悉&6&l机械动力&r,这些任务应该能帮助你学习这个模组.对于许多&e物品&f和&6机器&r,都有一个”思考”选项!查看&e物品&r时按住W键,可以观看一个示意图,它会教你理解这个&e物品&f或&6机器&r.\\n\\n相信我,你会想学习&6&l机械动力&r的,它超级有用!\\n\\n首先,你需要&8安山合金&r,而且需要很多.\\n&7[Most Players will already know of lCreate especially its billions of Addons! Not that many Mods have whole Modpacks based around them! \\n\\nIf you aren't used to lCreate, these Quests should help you to learn the Mod. And with many Items and Machines there is a Ponder Option! Hold W while viewing the Item to watch a schematic that will teach you to understand the Item or Machine. \\n\\nAnd trust me, you'll want to learn lCreate, it is super useful! \\n\\nTo start you'll need Andesite and lots of it.]&f"]
	quest.57A7A5C79389A96A.title: "&6&l机械动力&r&7[lCreate]&f"
	quest.5979DE0E2BA3DAE5.quest_desc: ["&7铁轨&r是……嗯,就是你用来移动&5列车&r的东西!\\n\\n你需要将2个&7&a铁粒&f&r&6部署&r到一个&8&a石台阶&f&r上,然后用&6&a金属冲压机&f&r&6按压&r它来获得1个铁轨.\\n\\n这将是你要放置的第一个方块,以便获得&5列车&r,因为放置&5火车站&r需要它.\\n\\n不过它们有一些限制,它们不能以陡峭的角度转弯或爬升.你需要4个方块的空间才能让&7铁轨&r上升一个方块的高度.转弯就更糟了!这么说吧,如果你想用&7铁轨&r做一个完美的圆,它的直径需要18个方块.\\n&7[Train Tracks are... well what you'll use to move Trains! \\n\\nYou'll need to Deploy 2 Iron Nuggets onto a Stone Slab, then Press it with a Metal Press to get 1. \\n\\nThese will be the first Block you place in order to get Trains as it will be needed to place Train Stations. \\n\\nThey have some limitations though, they can't go at steep angles to turn, or elevate. You'll need 4 Blocks of space to get up a Block with Train Tracks. To turn it is even worse! Let's just say, if you want a perfect circle with Train Tracks, it'll need a diameter of 18 Blocks.]&f"]
	quest.5979DE0E2BA3DAE5.title: "&7铁轨&7[Train Tracks]&f"
	quest.5B36DE3826F26963.quest_desc: ["&d旋转动力&r是&6&l机械动力&r中最重要也最令人困惑的部分.\\n\\n所有机器都需要某种&d旋转动力&r才能工作,但它是什么,我们如何使用它？\\n\\n&d旋转动力&r简单来说就是我们的机器在运动.像传动杆和齿轮这样的方块会将&d旋转动力&r传递到我们的机器上.\\n\\n说到传动杆,那是我们&d旋转动力&r的起点.它们可以直线放置,彼此相邻.\\n\\n当一个&8传动杆&r运动时,所有连接到它(在同一轴上)的&8传动杆&r都会随之运动.\\n\\n合成2个&8&a安山合金&f&r来制作8个&8传动杆&r.\\n&7[Rotational Power is the most important and confusing part of lCreate. \\n\\nAll Machines will need some sort of Rotational Power to work, but what is it and how do we use it? \\n\\nRotational Power is simply our Machines moving. Blocks like Shafts and Cogs will move that Rotational Power to our Machines. \\n\\nTalking about Shafts, that is our start to Rotational Power. They can be placed in a straight line, next to each other. \\n\\nWhen one Shaft is moved, all Shafts connected to it (on the same axis) will move with it. \\n\\nCraft 2 Andesite Alloys to create 8 Shafts.]&f"]
	quest.5B36DE3826F26963.title: "&d&l旋转动力&7[lRotational Power]&f"
	quest.5DC892BA79EB52EC.quest_desc: ["&6搅拌器&r可以做很多不同的配方,但所有配方都需要在它下面放一个&8盆&r!\\n\\n我们可以&6混合&r,这会将&b流体&f和&e物品&f结合成新的&e物品&r.就像烘焙一样!\\n\\n&6酿造&r可以将正确的&b流体&f和&e物品&r结合制成药水流体.然后可以将它们舀进&a玻璃瓶&f中得到药水.不过你需要来自&c烈焰人燃烧室&r的热量才能&6酿造&r.\\n\\n最后是&6&a自动搅拌&f&r.对于普通玩家来说,这可能是一个令人困惑的说法,但相信我,它没那么糟.&6无序合成&r是一种可以用任何图案摆放原料来制作的配方.\\n\\n就像给羊毛染色,染料和羊毛可以放在工作台的任何位置.甚至是&d寂静装备&f的部件和图案!\\n&7[The Mixer can do quite a few different Recipes but all will need a Basin below it! \\n\\nWe can Mix, this combines Liquids and Items into new Items. Like Baking! \\n\\nBrewing can combine the right Liquids and Items to make Liquid Potions. These can then be scooped out into Empty Bottles to get Potions. You'll need Heat from a Blaze Burner to Brew though. \\n\\nLast is Automated Shapeless Crafting. To the normal Player this might be a confusing statement but trust me it ain't that bad. Shapeless Crafting is a Recipe that can be made with the ingredients in any pattern. \\n\\nLike Dying Wool, the Dye and Wool can be anywhere in the Crafting Table. Or even Silent Gear parts and patterns!]&f"]
	quest.5DC892BA79EB52EC.title: "&6&a动力搅拌器&f&7[Mechanical Mixer]&f"
	quest.5DD6631F5996BA71.quest_desc: ["&9&a水车&f&r是简单的自动&d旋转动力&r发生器.\\n\\n只需放置它们,并让&9水&r以特定方向流过它们.如果水流过两侧,它就不会转动,而&9水&r流动的方向决定了&9&a水车&f&r&d旋转&r的方向.\\n\\n&a普通&f的&9&a水车&f&r只有1个方块大小,提供一点速度但应力单位很少.\\n\\n&9大型&a水车&f&r占据3x3区域,提供更多的应力单位,只是速度较低.\\n\\n你可以同时使用两者来获得相同的应力单位和速度!\\n&7[Water Wheels are simple automatic Rotational Power generators. \\n\\nSimply place them down, and have Water run over them in a certain direction. If it flows over both sides, it won't move, and the direction the Water flows determines where the Water Wheel Rotates to. \\n\\nThe normal Water Wheel is just 1 Block big and provides a bit of Speed but with minimal Stress Units. \\n\\nThe Large Water Wheel takes up 3x3 area and grants more Stress Units, just at a lower Speed. \\n\\nYou can use both together to get the same Stress Units and Speed!]&f"]
	quest.5DD6631F5996BA71.title: "&9&a水车&f&7[Water Wheels]&f"
	quest.6353A39CBEE599A0.quest_desc: ["你喜欢合并库存,并用几个简单的&6机器&r来查看和交互所有这些库存,类似于&b&l应用能源2&r和&7&l&d精妙存储&f&r吗？\\n\\n那么,你需要一些&e库存连接器&r!\\n\\n&e库存连接器&r可以放置在&e打包机&r上,以连接到&e打包机&r所连接的库存.首次放置时,会创建一个新的&e库存网络&r.\\n\\n这些可以连接到箱子、木桶,甚至是&e储物库&r!\\n\\n你也可以手持&e库存连接器&r&a右击&f另一个&e库存连接器&r,将它们调谐到同一个&e网络&r.当新的&e库存连接器&r被放置到另一个&e打包机&r上时,它的库存方块将被添加到同一个&e网络&r中.\\n\\n如果你想与这些&e网络&r交互,你将需要其他方块!\\n&7[You like combining Inventories and making a way of viewing and interacting with all those Inventories with a few simple Machines similar to lAE2 and lSophisticated Storage? \\n\\nThen, you'll need some Stock Links! \\n\\nStock Links can be placed on Packagers to connect to the Inventory the Packager is connected to. When first placed, a new Stock Network will be created. \\n\\nThese can connect to Chests, Barrels, and even Vaults! \\n\\nYou can also Right Click another Stock Link with a Stock Link in hand to tune them to the same Network. When the new Stock Link is placed onto another Packager, its Inventory Block will be added to the same Network. \\n\\nIf you'd like to Interact with these Networks you'll need other Blocks!]&f"]
	quest.6353A39CBEE599A0.title: "&e库存连接器&7[Stock Link]&f"
	quest.64860340A5BEBAB9.quest_desc: ["&e桌布&r既可以用来展示&e物品&r,也可以用来出售&e物品&r!\\n\\n要建立一个商店,请完成上一个任务中的所有步骤:放置&e库存连接器&f、&e库存交易器&r,以及一个坐在座位或&c烈焰人燃烧室&r上的生物.\\n\\n现在使用&e桌布&r与生物或&c烈焰人燃烧室&r交互,这将把&e桌布&r绑定到那个&e库存交易器&r上.\\n\\n放下&e桌布&r,你就可以把想出售的&e物品&r放在上面,价格放在下面.\\n\\n当有人购买一个&e物品&r时,它会向&e库存连接器&r发送一条消息,该连接器将&e打包&f购买的&e物品&r并收取价格.\\n&7[Table Cloths can either be used to show off Items, or to sell off Items! \\n\\nTo set up a Shop, do all the steps from the previous Quest: placing Stock Links, Stock Tickers, and a Mob on a Seat or Blaze Burner. \\n\\nNow use a Table Cloth to Interact with the Mob or Blaze Burner, this will bind the Table Cloth to that Stock Ticker. \\n\\nPlace down the Table Cloth and you'll be able to place the Items you want to sell on top, and the price below. \\n\\nWhen someone buys an Item, it will send a message to the Stock Link, which will Package the Items bought and take the price.]&f"]
	quest.64860340A5BEBAB9.quest_subtitle: "使用桌布&7[With Table Cloths]&f"
	quest.64860340A5BEBAB9.title: "商店&7[Shops]&f"
	quest.64FF7118E29931C0.quest_desc: ["在我们讨论可以从&6石磨&r获得的许多&e物品&r之前,我们先来谈谈如何使用它!\\n\\n首先,它需要一些&d旋转动力&r,别担心,只需要一点点.\\n\\n然后,你需要将想要&6研磨&r的&e物品&r丢进&6石磨&r的顶部.在它被&6研磨&r之后,只需&a右击&f&6石磨&r取出你的&e物品&r.\\n\\n现在,我们可以从&6石磨&r获得哪些&e物品&r呢？我们可以从几乎所有的花中获得染料,我们可以将&7石头&r粉碎成沙砾,或者其他类似&7石头&r的方块粉碎成类似的沙砾物品.你甚至可以从小麦中获得&a小麦粉&f!\\n&7[Before we get into the many Items we can get from the Millstone, let's talk about how to use it! \\n\\nFirst, it will need some Rotational Power, don't worry it only needs a little. \\n\\nThen, you'll need to Drop the Item you want Milled, into the top of the Millstone. After it gets Milled, just Right Click the Millstone to take out your Items. \\n\\nNow, what Items can we get from the Millstone? We can get Dyes from pretty much every Flower, we can crush Stone into Gravel or other Stone like Blocks into similar Gravel Items. You can even get Wheat Flour from Wheat!]&f"]
	quest.64FF7118E29931C0.title: "&6石磨&7[Millstone]&f"
	quest.6637B33E9D474D5F.quest_desc: ["&a转速控制器&f是机械动力中的核心进度物品.它允许你控制和微调旋转速度,这是许多高级装置所必需的.\\n&7[The Rotation Speed Controller is a core progression item in Create. It allows you to control and fine-tune rotational speed, which is required for many advanced contraptions.]&f"]
	quest.6637B33E9D474D5F.title: "&e&a转速控制器&f&7[Rotation Speed Controller]&f"
	quest.672F9CF5B0E626F1.quest_desc: ["&e打包机&r是&6&l机械动力&r中全新且非常重要的&6机器&r.为了使用更新中的几乎所有内容,我们都需要一个&e打包机&r.\\n将我们新发现的&e纸板&r合成成&a块&f纸板.不,这些还不是&e箱子&r,而且它们肯定什么都不做.\\n\\n嗯,除了合成我们的&e打包机&r!然后将&e打包机&r放置在有库存的方块上,比如箱子或木桶.当它的一侧变成像墙一样的外观时,你就知道它连接成功了.\\n\\n然后,当接收到&4&a红石信号&f&r时,它会将库存中的所有&e物品&r拉入一个&e包裹&r中!稍后再详细介绍!\\n\\n&e包裹&r然后可以用手或&e传送带&r取出.你也可以将&e包裹&r送回&e打包机&r,将&e物品&r放回库存中.\\n\\n如果你在&e打包机&r上放置并命名一个告示牌,它会给所有它制作的&e包裹&r一个地址.\\n&7[Packagers are the new and very important Machine for lCreate. In order to use pretty much everything from the Update we'll need a Packager. \\nCombine some of our new-found Cardboard to make a Block of Cardboard. No, these aren't Boxes yet and they certainly don't do anything. \\n\\nWell besides Crafting our Packager! The Packager will then be placed onto a Block with an Inventory, like Chest or Barrel. You'll know it is connected when one of the sides changes to appear like a wall. \\n\\nThen, when given a Redstone Signal it will pull all Items within the Inventory into a Package! More on that later! \\n\\nThe Packages can then be pulled out by Hand or Belt. You can also send Packages back into the Packager to put the Items back into an Inventory. \\n\\nIf you place and name a Sign on the Packager it will give all Packages that it makes an Address.]&f"]
	quest.672F9CF5B0E626F1.title: "&e打包机&7[Packagers]&f"
	quest.67A46ED73E488CEE.quest_desc: ["&d换向齿轮&r的工作原理类似于&d离合器&r,连接到我们的系统并由&4红石&r供能.\\n\\n不过,与停止&d旋转动力&r不同,&d换向齿轮&r会改变其方向!\\n\\n如果动力&d换向齿轮&r的输入是&e&o顺时针&r,那么输出将是&9&o逆时针&r,反之亦然.\\n&7[Gearshifts work similar to a Clutch by connecting to our Systems and being powered by Redstone. \\n\\nInstead of stopping Rotational Power though, the Gearshift will change its Direction! \\n\\nIf it is going Clockwise into the powered Gearshift, it will come out Counter-Clockwise, and vice versa.]&f"]
	quest.67A46ED73E488CEE.title: "&d换向齿轮&7[Gearshift]&f"
	quest.6893D537716AA748.quest_desc: ["&d齿轮&r(&d齿轮&r)是使用&d旋转动力&r所需的下一类方块!它们可以连接到&8传动杆&r或其他&d齿轮&r来传递&d旋转动力&r.\\n\\n&d齿轮&r有两种版本:普通&d齿轮&f和&d大型齿轮&r.在&d旋转动力&r的意义上,它们的作用相同,但也有一些变化!\\n普通&d齿轮&r可以连接到与其相邻的其他&d齿轮&r.这会将&d旋转动力&r传递到一个完全不同的方向.当这种情况发生时,第二个&d齿轮&r的方向将会反转.如果第一个&d齿轮&r是&e&o顺时针&r旋转,第二个将是&9&o逆时针&r旋转.\\n\\n&d大型齿轮&r比&d齿轮&r使用起来稍微困难一些.它们不能连接到相邻的其他&d大型齿轮&r,而是只能连接到与其对角放置的&d齿轮&r!\\n\\n大多数&6机器&r都需要通过连接的&d齿轮&r提供&d旋转动力&r.如果&6机器&r有一个内部的&d齿轮&r,你会认出来,那就是必须被转动才能使用&6机器&r的部分.\\n&7[Cogwheels (Cogs) are the next Block needed to use Rotational Power! They can connect to Shafts or other Cogs to move the Rotational Power. \\n\\nThere is two versions of Cogs: regular Cogs and Large Cogs. They will both act the same in the sense of Rotational Power but there is also a few changes! \\nRegular Cogs can connect to other Cogs adjacent to them. This will move the Rotational Power into a whole different direction. When this happens the direction of the second Cog will be reversed. If the first Cog is rotating Clockwise, the second one will rotate Counter-Clockwise. \\n\\nLarge Cogs are a little more difficult to use than Cogs. They can't connect to other Large Cogs adjacent, rather they can only connect to Cogs that are diagonal to them! \\n\\nMost Machines will need Rotational Power from connecting Cogs. You'll recognize if the Machine has an internal Cog, that is what must be moved in order to use the Machine. ]&f"]
	quest.6893D537716AA748.quest_subtitle: "我就叫它们齿轮&7[I just call them Cogs]&f"
	quest.6893D537716AA748.title: "&d齿轮&r!&7[Cogwheels!]&f"
	quest.69EE22CB4FF1E591.quest_desc: ["&a装置&r非常难以理解,但基本上它是将不同的方块和&6机器&r组合成一个运动系统的艺术.\\n\\n你需要&6机器&r来实际移动&a装置&r,比如&a线性底盘&r,你需要工作的&6机器&r,比如&6钻头&r,你还需要&a粘液球&r把一切都粘在一起!\\n\\n一旦全部&a粘合&r,当&d旋转动力&r被提供给&a装置&r的运动&6机器&r时,它就应该运动了.\\n&7[Contraptions are very difficult to understand but pretty much it is the art of combining different Blocks and Machines into one moving systems. \\n\\nYou'll need Machines to actually move the Contraption like Linear Chasis, you'll need the Machines you want to work like Drills, and you'll need Glue to hold it all together! \\n\\nOnce it is all Glued it should move when Rotational Power is given to the moving Machine of the Contraption.]&f"]
	quest.69EE22CB4FF1E591.title: "&a&l装置&7[lContraptions]&f"
	quest.71B1B53A03A16296.quest_desc: ["&b&a移动式流体接口&f&r与使用&b&a流体储罐&f&r的&a装置&r一起使用.\\n\\n为了访问&b&a流体储罐&f&r,你需要两个&b&a移动式流体接口&f&r,一个连接到&a装置&r,一个连接到&b&a流体管道&f&r.\\n\\n&b&a移动式流体接口&f&r需要在会合点之间有1或2个方块的间隙才能工作.\\n\\n如果我们具备了所有这些条件,连接到&a装置&r的&b&a移动式流体接口&f&r会停止&a装置&r,以便从第二个&b&a移动式流体接口&f&r中吸入或排出&b流体&r,将其添加到&a装置&r内的&b&a流体储罐&f&r中.\\n&7[Portable Fluid Interfaces are used with Contraptions that are using Fluid Tanks. \\n\\nIn order to access the Fluid Tanks you'll need two Portable Fluid Interfaces, one connected to the Contraption and one connected to Fluid Pipes. \\n\\nThe Portable Fluid Interfaces will need a 1 or 2 Block gap between a meeting point in order for them to work. \\n\\nIf we have all that, the Portable Fluid Interface connected to the Contraption will stop the Contraption to either take Fluids in or out from the second Portable Fluid Interface to add it to the Fluid Tanks within the Contraption.]&f"]
	quest.71B1B53A03A16296.title: "&b&a移动式流体接口&f&7[Portable Fluid Interfaces]&f"
	quest.7242F591DA474B37.quest_desc: ["&b流体&f和&b液体&r并非&6&l机械动力&r每个方面都最重要,但幸运的是,你很可能无论如何都会遇到它们!\\n\\n你需要学习&b&a流体物流&f&r的艰难道路才能使用和移动它们.\\n\\n而要开始,你需要&c铜&r!\\n&7[Fluids and Liquids aren't the most important in every aspect of lCreate, but luck is, you'll most likely run into them anyways! \\n\\nYou'll need to learn the difficult path of Fluid Logistics in order to use and move them. \\n\\nAnd to start, you'll need Copper!]&f"]
	quest.7242F591DA474B37.title: "&b&l&a流体物流&f&7[lFluid Logistics]&f"
	quest.72537968598AB884.quest_desc: ["&6工程师护目镜&r非常适合你们这些无所不知的小家伙.\\n\\n佩戴时,它会告诉你方块或&6机器&r几乎所有的信息!\\n\\n应力表会告诉你提供了多少应力以及它能承受多少.速度表会告诉你系统中速度是多少.\\n\\n&d&a蒸汽锅炉&f&r会告诉你它们有多大、有多少&9水&r以及有多少热量.\\n\\n其他&6机器&r,比如&6部署器&r或&6&a动力辊压机&f&r,会显示正在消耗多少应力单位.\\n&7[Engineer's Goggles are perfect for you little know-it-alls. \\n\\nWhen worn it will tell just about everything the Block or Machine has to tell! \\n\\nStressometers will tell how much Stress is given and how much it can take. Speedometers will tell how much Speed is within your system. \\n\\nSteam Boilers will tell how big, how much Water, and how much Heat they have. \\n\\nOther Machines, like Deployers or Mechanical Presses, will show how much Stress Units is being used up.]&f"]
	quest.72537968598AB884.title: "&6工程师护目镜&7[Engineer's Goggles]&f"
	quest.72C7698072BF0F1D.quest_desc: ["&d&a手摇曲柄&f&r是最简单也是最差的&d旋转动力&r生成方式.\\n\\n当你按住&a右击&f时,它会&e&o顺时针&r转动,如果你按住潜行键&a右击&f,它会&9&o逆时针&r转动.\\n\\n它只提供极少量的应力单位,并且在你停止按住后会停止.\\n&7[The Hand Crank is the simplest and worst form of Rotational Power generation. \\n\\nWhen you hold Right Click it'll move Clockwise and if you hold Shift Right Click it will move Counter-Clockwise. \\n\\nIt only gives a tiny bit of Stress Units and will stop after you quit holding it.]&f"]
	quest.72C7698072BF0F1D.quest_subtitle: "手动动力!&7[Manual Power!]&f"
	quest.72C7698072BF0F1D.title: "&d&a手摇曲柄&f&7[Hand Crank]&f"
	quest.72DCE154E1714890.quest_desc: [
		"要单独查看&6&a动力锯&f&r,请查看第二页!这一页讨论它们在&a装置&r中的使用.\\n\\n当在&a装置&r中移动时,&6&a动力锯&f&r会破坏任何它接触到的树木!它需要击中树的底部,并破坏树最低部分的所有原木.\\n\\n一旦它破坏了那些原木,整棵树就会被砍伐成物品形式.\\n\\n如果&a装置&r有库存,树的部件将被收集到其中.如果没有,树将留在自然中……在地面上.\\n&7[To see Mechanical Saws on their own, check out the second Page! This one talks about them in Contraptions. \\n\\nWhen moved in a Contraption, the Mechanical Saw will break any Tree that it comes in contact with! It will need to hit the bottom of the Tree and break all of the Logs on the lowest part of the Tree. \\n\\nOnce it breaks those Logs, the entire Tree will be cut down into Item form. \\n\\nIf the Contraption has an Inventory, the Tree parts will be collected into it. If not, the Tree will remain in nature... on the ground.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&6&a动力锯&f&r在不用于&a装置&r时也可以执行其他任务.相反,它们可以被放置下来并与&d旋转动力&r一起使用.\\n\\n&6锯&r也可以砍伐它们附近的树木.是的,它们仍然需要砍伐最低的原木.\\n\\n但它也可以用作&7切石机&r/伐木机!要这样使用它,需要像平常一样面朝上放置.\\n\\n然后,我们可以用手(戴上正确的防护)或通过&e传送带&r给它喂入方块.原木会被剥皮,石质方块会被切割.\\n\\n如果方块在切割机中有多个配方,你可以通过将该方块放入&6&a动力锯&f&r的过滤器中来筛选你想要的配方.\\n&7[The Mechanical Saw can also do other tasks when not used in a Contraption. Instead they can be placed down and used with Rotational Power. \\n\\nThe Saw can also cut down Trees that are near them. Yes, they'll still need to cut down the lowest Logs. \\n\\nBut it can be used as a Stonecutter/Woodcutter as well! To use it like that it'll need to be placed faced up, like normal. \\n\\nThen, we can either feed it Blocks from our Hands (with the correct protection on) or through Belts. Logs will be Stripped and Stone Blocks will be Cut. \\n\\nIf the Block has multiple Recipes through the Cutter, you can Filter which one you want by placing that Block in the Mechanical Saw's Filter.]&f"
	]
	quest.72DCE154E1714890.title: "&6&a动力锯&f&7[Mechanical Saw]&f"
	quest.737DC37E4310090C.quest_desc: ["&8链式传送带&r本身做不了什么.它们需要另一个&8链式传送带&f、&8链条&f和&d旋转动力&r!\\n&8链式传送带&r需要附近有另一个&8链式传送带&r,以便用&8链条&r连接它们.\\n\\n&8链条&r需要&a右击&f一个&8链式传送带&r,然后同样操作你想连接的另一个传送带.\\n\\n一旦其中一个被提供&d旋转动力&r,&8链条&r将以相同的速度移动.不用担心方向,会有2条&8链条&r!\\n\\n当&8链条&r移动时,你可以用&6扳手&r连接到它们上面,随着&8链条&r移动,你可以按Shift键或切换物品来从&8链条&r上下来.\\n\\n你也可以把&e包裹&r放在上面,但如果没有下一个任务中描述的&e物品&r,它们只会绕圈转!\\n&7[Chain Conveyors won't do much on their own. They need another Chain Conveyor, Chains, and Rotational Power! \\nChain Conveyors will need another Chain Conveyor near by in order to attach to them with Chains. \\n\\nThe Chains will need to be Right Clicked onto 1 Chain Conveyor then done the same to another you want to connect it to. \\n\\nOnce, one is given Rotational Power, the Chains will move at the same Speed. Don't worry about Direction, there'll be 2 Chains! \\n\\nWhen the Chains are a moving, you can connect to them with a Wrench to move with the Chains, you can either press Shift or switch Items to drop off the Chain. \\n\\nYou can also place Packages on them, but without the Item described in the next Quest, they will just go around in a circle!]&f"]
	quest.737DC37E4310090C.title: "&8链式传送带&7[Chain Conveyor]&f"
	quest.754B8F1FBCD983C5.quest_desc: ["&e库存标记器&r可以通过手持&e库存标记器&r&a右击&f&e库存链接&r来设置到&e网络&r中.\\n\\n然后,放下&e库存标记器&r,并通过在附近放置一个&c烈焰人燃烧器&r或让一个生物坐在&e座椅&r上来为其提供一个&e库存管理员&r.\\n\\n你可以通过他们标志性的&a绿色&r护目镜来识别他们是&e库存管理员&r.现在我们可以&a右击&f&e库存管理员&r来查看并从我们的&e网络&r中订购&e物品&r.\\n\\n当你订购&e物品&r时,它们会被放入&e库存链接&r下方&e打包机&r生成的&e包裹&r中.\\n&7[Stock Tickers can be set to the Network by Right Clicking the Stock Link with the Stock Ticker in Hand. \\n\\nThen, place down the Stock Ticker and give it a Stock Keeper by either placing down a Blaze Burner or a Mob on a Seat nearby. \\n\\nYou'll know they are a Stock Keeper by their stereotypical Green Visor. We can now Right Click the Stock Keeper to view and order Items from our Network. \\n\\nWhen you order Items, they'll be placed into a Package from a Packager below the Stock Link.]&f"]
	quest.754B8F1FBCD983C5.title: "&e库存标记器&7[Stock Ticker]&f"
	quest.75B14A09FE39EDDA.quest_desc: ["你喜欢你的&a机械装置&r只走直线吗？那么,&a&a起重机取物器&f&r就是你的完美选择!\\n\\n在你希望&a机械装置&r移动的直线上放下&a&a起重机杆&f&r,并为其提供&d旋转动力&r.\\n\\n然后,在&a门架&f和&a传动杆&r顶部放下你的&a&a起重机取物器&f&r,它会随之移动.\\n\\n你可以在&a&a起重机取物器&f&r顶部&a粘合&r方块和&6机器&r,让它们也一起移动!\\n\\n&a&a起重机杆&f&r可以通过给予&4&a红石信号&f&r来停止.你有没有注意到它们看起来像理发店的那些柱子？\\n&7[Do you like your Contraptions going only on a straight line? Then, the Gantry Carriage is perfect for you! \\n\\nPlace down the Gantry Shafts down in the line you wish your Contraption to go and give it Rotational Power. \\n\\nThen, place down your Gantry Carriage on top of the Gantry and Shaft and it will move along with it. \\n\\nYou can Glue Blocks and Machines on top of the Gantry Carriage to also move with it! \\n\\nThe Gantry Shafts can be stopped by giving it a Redstone Signal. Do you also notice how they look like those poles Barbershops have?]&f"]
	quest.75B14A09FE39EDDA.quest_subtitle: "理发店旋转柱&7[Barbershop Poles]&f"
	quest.75B14A09FE39EDDA.title: "&a&a起重机取物器&f&7[Gantry Carriage]&f"
	quest.75CBB5BD8C1DFEA1.quest_desc: ["&8混合盆&r与&e仓库&r类似,但可以容纳&e物品&r和&b流体&r.\\n\\n这对于使用&6&a动力搅拌器&f&r进行混合和酿造会很有帮助.\\n\\n还有使用&6&a动力辊压机&f&r进行自动合成!\\n&7[The Basin is similar to the Depot, but can hold Items and Fluids. \\n\\nThis will be helpful for using the Mechanical Mixer to Mix and Brew. \\n\\nAnd with the Mechanical Press to Autocraft!]&f"]
	quest.75CBB5BD8C1DFEA1.title: "&8混合盆&7[Basin]&f"
	quest.76CBFA38D021AC95.quest_desc: ["&d风车&r比&9&a水车&f&r稍微复杂一些,但它们也提供了更多的自定义选项,当然还有速度和应力单位!\\n\\n首先,你需要&d风车&r的核心,&d&a风车轴承&f&r.这个方块会输出&d旋转动力&r.它也是我们用来启动&d风车&r的部件!\\n\\n然后,你需要制作实际&d风车&r部分的方块.方块会自动粘附到&d轴承&r上,但对于&d风车&r的其余部分,你需要使用&a粘液球&r.除了&d&a改良风车叶片&f&r,那些会自动附着!\\n\\n我们还需要至少8个类似&d&a改良风车叶片&f&r的方块,比如&d&a改良风车叶片&f&r或羊毛.我们拥有的越多,&d风车&r旋转得越快!\\n\\n一旦全部设置好,只需用空手&a右击&f&d轴承&r即可启动它.\\n&7[Windmills are a little more complicated than Water Wheels, but they also come with more customization and of course Speed and Stress Units! \\n\\nFirst, you'll need the heart of the Windmill, the Windmill Bearing. This Block will send the Rotational Power out of it. It is also what we'll use to turn on the Windmill! \\n\\nThen, you'll need the Blocks to make the actual Windmill part. Blocks will automatically stick to the Bearing, but to the rest of the Windmill you'll need Glue. Besides Windmill Sails, those attach automatically! \\n\\nWe'll also need atleast 8 Windmill Sail like Blocks, those being the Windmill Sails or Wool. The more we have, the faster the Windmill spins! \\n\\nOnce it is all set, just Right Click the Bearing with an Empty Hand to start it up.]&f"]
	quest.76CBFA38D021AC95.title: "&d风车&7[Windmills]&f"
	quest.77382D4114E901CB.quest_desc: ["&b&a软管滑轮&f&r用于拾取和放置完整的&b流体&r源方块,是的,不仅仅是&9水&r.\\n\\n首先,用一侧的&8传动杆&r设置&b软管&r实际下降或上升的距离.可以使用&6齿轮&f、&8传动杆&r或&d&a手摇曲柄&f&r,后者最简单.\\n\\n然后,在&b&a软管滑轮&f&r的另一侧,我们可以放置一些&b&a流体管道&f&r.使用&b&a机械泵&f&r,我们可以选择&b&a软管滑轮&f&r是拾取&b流体&r源方块还是放置它们.\\n\\n&b&a软管滑轮&f&r的库存容量只有1.5桶或1500mB,但&b流体&r可以被&b管道&r输送到其他库存或&b储罐&r中!\\n\\n如果&9水&r源是无限的,&b&a软管滑轮&f&r不会取出源方块,但会持续取出&b流体&r.\\n\\n这也适用于&c熔岩&r源方块,但它们不是无限的.所以你可能想去&c&l&a下界&f&r看看,因为那里几乎是无限的!\\n&7[The Hose Pulley is used to take and place full Source Blocks of Fluids, yes not just Water. \\n\\nFirst, set how far the Hose actually goes down or up with the Shaft at one side. Either with a Cog, Shaft, or Hand Crank which is easiest. \\n\\nThen, on the other side of the Hose Pulley we can put some Fluid Pipes. With Mechanical Pumps we can choose whether the Hose Pulley picks up Fluid Sources or place them down. \\n\\nThe Hose Pulley only has an Inventory of 1.5 Buckets or 1500mB, but the Fluids can be Piped into other Inventories or Tanks! \\n\\nIf the Water Source is infinite, the Hose Pulley won't take out Source Blocks, but will keep taking Fluid out. \\n\\nThis will also work with Lava Source Blocks, but those aren't infinite. So you might want to check out lThe Nether for that as it is pretty much infinite there!]&f"]
	quest.77382D4114E901CB.title: "&b&a软管滑轮&f&7[Hose Pulley]&f"
	quest.77BE3D9D274F72F1.quest_desc: ["&5火车站&r是&5列车&r最重要的方块!我们需要它们来制造&5列车&f、分解&5列车&r以及为它们安排行程!\\n\\n要使用它们,你需要用它们选择一条&7铁轨&r.手持&5火车站&r并&a右击&f一条&7铁轨&r.\\n\\n我不知道&5火车站&r可以放置的最大距离,但至少有10个方块!(我没有那么大的空间来测试).\\n\\n放置后,你可以使用顶部的文本栏为其重命名.\\n\\n你也可以点击”&a新建&f列车”来开始制作你的第一辆&5列车&r.点击后,其中一条&7铁轨&r会显示为&9蓝色&r,这是你可以放置&5转向架&r的&7铁轨&r.\\n\\n用&5列车外壳&r&a右击&f那条&7铁轨&r来制作一个&5转向架&r,也就是&5列车车轮&r.&a右击&f实际的车轮可以改变其设计.然后你可以...\\n&7[Train Stations are the most important Blocks for Trains! We need them for making Trains, breaking down Trains, and Scheduling them! \\n\\nTo use them, you'll need to select a Train Track with them. Hold the Train Station in your Hand and Right Click a Train Track. \\n\\nI don't know the max distance a Train Station can be placed, it is atleast 10 Blocks! (I don't have that much room to test). \\n\\nOnce placed you can Rename it with the Text Bar at the top. \\n\\nYou can also Click \"Create New Train\", to start making your first Train. After you Clicked it, one of the Tracks will appear Blue, this is the Track you can place Boogeys on. \\n\\nRight Click that Track with a Train Casing to make a Boogey, AKA Train Wheels. Right Click the actual Wheels to change its design. Then you can...]&f"]
	quest.77BE3D9D274F72F1.title: "&5火车站&7[Train Stations]&f"
	quest.78656C89EEE80DB5.quest_desc: ["&e&a黄铜隧道&f&r的工作方式类似于&e&a安山岩隧道&f&r,只是配置选项多得多!\\n\\n首先,我们现在有了过滤器!这些是按面设置的:如果你过滤输入面,只有该过滤器中的&e物品&r才被允许通过&e隧道&r.如果你过滤输出面,那么只有那些&e物品&r会从其对应的面输出.\\n\\n现在,我们还可以将&e&a黄铜隧道&f&r串联在一起.这将允许它们接收所有相同的输入,但将物品过滤到特定的&e传送带&r上!\\n\\n在&e隧道&r的顶部,我们可以找到更改其分发模式的选项.我不会解释得太详细,我们的任务书空间有限,我会做个总结!\\n\\n分流:会根据物品将要去的&e传送带&r数量平均分配&e物品&r堆叠.&a强制分流&f:确保每条&e传送带&r获得相同数量的物品,而普通分流可能会跳过一些.&a轮询&f:会在每条&e传送带&r之间交替分配单个物品.&a强制轮询调度&f:不会跳过某些&e物品&r,而是会等待,确保每个输出都有机会!优先最近:会将&e物品&r发送到最近的输出.随机:将&e物品&r随机发送到不同的输出.同步输入:只有当每个&e&a黄铜隧道&f&r都有一个&e物品&r等待输入时才会输出.\\n&7[Brass Tunnels work like Andesite Tunnels just with so many more configurations! \\n\\nFirst, we now get Filters! These are per side: if you Filter the Input side, only that Filter Item will be allowed to move throught the Tunnel. If you Filter the Output sides, then only those Items will come out of its side. \\n\\nNow we can also line Brass Tunnels together. This will allow them to take all the same Inputs but Filter them out to certain Belts! \\n\\nAt the top of the Tunnel we'll find the option to change its Distribution Modes. I won't explain them in too much detail, our Quests have limited space, instead I'll summarize! \\n\\nSplit: will split the Item stacks evenly per how many Belts it will go to. Forced Split: will make sure every Belt will get an even amount, while normal Split might skip some. Round Robin: will alternate individually between each Belt. Forced Round Robin: won't skip some Items and instead will wait, everyone gets a turn! Prefer Nearest: will send the Items to the closest Output. Randomize: it sends the Items randomly to different Outputs. Synchronize Inputs: will only Output when every Brass Tunnel has an Item waiting to Input.]&f"]
	quest.78656C89EEE80DB5.title: "&e&a黄铜隧道&f&7[Brass Tunnel]&f"
	quest.7C8CDD259495A31A.quest_desc: ["&e隧道&r在最基本的层面上,会覆盖你的&e传送带&r.这将使得&e物品&r无法被拾取,并且希望生物不会离开.\\n\\n如果你在与&e隧道&r所在的&e传送带&r垂直的方向放置另一条&e传送带&r,&e隧道&r会从&e物品&r堆叠中过滤出1个&e物品&r到垂直的&e传送带&r上,而其余的&e物品&r则留在第一条&e传送带&r上.\\n\\n如果只有1个&e物品&r,它会像正常一样通过&e隧道&r.\\n&7[Tunnels at the most basic level, will cover your Belts. This will make it so the Items can't be picked up, and hopefully the Mobs won't leave. \\n\\nIf you place another Belt moving perpendicular to the Belt the Tunnel is on, the Tunnel will filter 1 Item from the Stack of Items to the perpendicular Belt, while leaving the rest of the Items on the first Belt. \\n\\nIf there is just 1 Item, it will move through the Tunnel like normal.]&f"]
	quest.7C8CDD259495A31A.title: "&e&a安山岩隧道&f&7[Andesite Tunnel]&f"
	quest.7D67058592EE5958.quest_desc: ["&a加农炮&f会根据蓝图建造结构,从附近的箱子中获取材料,并使用火药作为燃料.\\n&7[The Cannon will build the structures from Schematics, taking materials from nearby chests and using gunpowder as fuel.]&f"]
	quest.7EEEEDD5FF31ACD3.quest_desc: ["&e&a智能溜槽&f&r是一个带有过滤选项的&e溜槽&r.\\n&7[The Smart Chute is a Chute with the options to Filter.]&f"]
	quest.7EEEEDD5FF31ACD3.title: "&e&a智能溜槽&f&7[Smart Chute]&f"
	quest.7F0F7111552F95A9.quest_desc: ["好了,我们有了完全组装好的&5列车&r,现在怎么使用它呢？\\n\\n如果你要控制它,你需要&a右击&f&5列车控制器&r.\\n\\n然后,你可以按住W键向前移动,或按住S键向后移动.不,&5列车&r不像汽车那样转弯,它们只是沿着&7铁轨&r行驶.\\n\\n向前行驶时,你会获得很多速度,你可以在取代你&a经验条&r的进度条中看到它.向后行驶不会提供那么多速度.\\n\\n如果你接近一个&5火车站&r并且没有以光速移动,你可以按住空格键让&5列车&f在&5车站&r停下.这对于拆卸它们甚至连接更多&5转向架&r很有帮助.\\n&7[Okay we got our fully Assembled Train, now how do we use it? \\n\\nIf you are Controlling it, you'll need to Right Click the Train Controls. \\n\\nThen, you can Hold W to move Forward or Hold S to go Backwards. No, Trains don't turn like Cars do, they just follow the Tracks. \\n\\nGoing Forward you'll pick up a lot of Speed, you can see it in the Bar that replaces your Experience Bar. Backwards won't give as much Speed. \\n\\nIf you are getting near a Train Station and not moving at the speed of light, you can Hold Space to stop the Train at the Station. This is helpful for disassembling them or even connecting more Boogeys.]&f"]
	quest.7F0F7111552F95A9.title: "控制你的&5列车&7[Controlling your Train]&f"
	quest.7F8E50FA436DB4E6.quest_desc: ["&d&a链式传动箱&f&r的作用类似于&e传送带&r,将一排&8传动杆&r彼此连接起来.\\n\\n不过,也有一些区别,比如&d&a链式传动箱&f&r可以用&6扳手&r旋转.它们也需要直接放置在其他&d链式传动箱&r旁边以保持&d旋转&r.\\n\\n不过,和&e传送带&r一样,它们保持与原始&8传动杆&r相同的速度和应力单位.而且它们保持相同的方向!\\n&7[Encased Chain Drives will act similar to Belts, by connecting Shafts to each other in a row. \\n\\nThere is quite a few differences though, like that Encased Chain Drives can be used with a Wrench to rotate. They also need to be placed directly next to other Chain Drives to keep Rotating. \\n\\nLike Belts though, they keep the same Speed and Stress Units as the original Shaft. Plus they keep the same direction!]&f"]
	quest.7F8E50FA436DB4E6.title: "&d&a链式传动箱&f&7[Encased Chain Drives]&f"
	task.0BD1BA7949BB5855.title: "&a动力活塞&f&7[Mechanical Pistons]&f"
	task.194776374F591632.title: "邮箱&7[Postboxes]&f"
	task.21C5C92ABD91D795.title: "座椅&7[Seats]&f"
	task.3AB6845819FF686F.title: "纸板包裹&7[Cardboard Packages]&f"
	task.45140DDB8CE40AC4.title: "桌布&7[Table Cloth]&f"
	task.6F72D8976359CFF9.title: "&a水车&f&7[Water Wheels]&f"
	task.727CBE88631AC9E4.title: "齿轮&7[Cogwheels]&f"
	quest.0000A88BB40B2149.quest_desc: ["Now before you get to the Chaos Island I recommend preparing, he may look like the Ender Dragon but this one is much more difficult. You'll want Draconic Weapons or Tools that do a lot of damage as those will make it easier. He will also do a crap-ton of damage good Armor like 难得素 or Meka-Suit will be recommended. (Also effects of Regeneration, Absorption, and Resistance will help you survive}. Don't worry you can always come back to fight another day if you aren't ready."]
	quest.0000A88BB40B2149.title: "你需要做好准备,这很艰难&7[It's tough you'll need to prepare]&f"
	quest.01612963DBBAC9A1.quest_desc: ["希望这能保护你.\\n&7[Hopefully this should protect you.]&f"]
	quest.01612963DBBAC9A1.title: "混沌胸甲&7[Chaotic Chestplate]&f"
	quest.0252B8F77A038D17.title: "&a飞龙自动进食模块&f&7[Wyvern Auto Feed Module]&f"
	quest.04695DA1BD3BF1B2.title: "&a混沌伤害模块&f&7[Chaotic Damage Module]&f"
	quest.0499A372F55D04C8.title: "&a神龙箭矢速度模块&f&7[Draconic Projectile Velocity Module]&f"
	quest.04BF68E4554D69AA.quest_desc: [
		"最后也是最好的第8级!你需要378个&a觉醒龙块&f和786个&a龙锭&f方块!值得吗？\\n&7[Last and the best one Tier 8! You'll need 378 Awakened Draconium Blocks and 786 Draconium Ingot Blocks! Is it worth it?]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_8off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_8on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.04BF68E4554D69AA.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f近乎无限&7[Stores: Near Infinite]&f"
	quest.04BF68E4554D69AA.title: "第8级&7[Tier 8]&f"
	quest.052E261F934AB439.quest_desc: ["也可以制作路径!\\n&7[Also can make Pathways!]&f"]
	quest.052E261F934AB439.title: "&a混沌锹&f&7[Chaotic Shovel]&f"
	quest.070F8045CC14B50D.title: "&a神龙箭矢穿透模块&f&7[Draconic Projectile Penetration Module]&f"
	quest.0817FD6E45C127E8.quest_desc: ["从技术上讲,这是可选的,但推荐!你可以使用更多的能量塔来输入和输出更多的OP!\\n&7[Technically this is optional but recommended! You can use more Pylons to take in and out more OP!]&f"]
	quest.0817FD6E45C127E8.title: "More Pylons {optional)"
	quest.0AE8B51D63327EC3.title: "&a混沌护盾回复模块&f&7[Chaotic Shield Recovery Module]&f"
	quest.0AE930BA037DC565.quest_desc: ["查看模块以了解更多关于如何使用和升级DE物品的信息!像普通弓一样通过射箭工作.每次射击会从弓本身消耗一定量的能量,所以是的,你至少需要&a能量模块&f.\\n&7[Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! Works as a normal Bow does by shooting arrows. Each shot takes an amount of Energy from the Bow itself, so yes you'll need Energy Modules atleast.]&f"]
	quest.0AE930BA037DC565.title: "&a飞龙弓&f&7[Wyvern Bow]&f"
	quest.0E487EACA837EA9B.title: "&a混沌护盾控制模块&f&7[Chaotic Shield Control Module]&f"
	quest.10690FDB9E892250.quest_desc: ["查看模块以了解更多关于如何使用和升级DE物品的信息!挥动它并击中某物.拜托,这是一把剑,我不能再解释了.\\n&7[Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! Swing it and hit something with it. Come on, it's a sword I can't explain it anymore.]&f"]
	quest.10690FDB9E892250.title: "&a飞龙剑&f&7[Wyvern Sword]&f"
	quest.106D08542AAFA166.quest_desc: [
		"战斗的第一阶段涉及打破维持&a混沌守卫&f护盾的水晶.在它们被摧毁之前,你无法伤害他.没有龙之武器,摧毁这些水晶并非易事.&a混沌守卫&f的火球可以削弱这个护盾,让你能够摧毁它.(是的,他需要向你射击/击中水晶).你会注意到当水晶易受伤害时会产生粒子效果,被击中时会发出声音.越接近毁灭,声音越低沉,水晶也会变得越暗.一旦它们被摧毁,你终于可以伤害他了!\\n&7[The first stage of the fight involves breaking the Crystals that hold the Chaos Guardians Shield. You can't hurt him until they are destroyed. Destroying these crystals is no easy task without a Draconic weapon. Chaos Guardian fire balls can weaken this shield allowing you to destroy it. (Yes, he will need too shoot at you/hitting the crystals). You'll notice particles being produced when it's vulnerable to damages and when hit will make a noise. The closer to destruction the deeper the noise and dimmer the Crystal will get. Once they are destroyed you can finally damage him!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_end_crystal.png width:150 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.106D08542AAFA166.title: "定位并摧毁14个&a守卫水晶&f&7[Locate and Destroy 14 Guardian Crystals]&f"
	quest.10E4ADA1D0063EB7.title: "&a混沌箭矢速度模块&f&7[Chaotic Projectile Velocity Module]&f"
	quest.120B403D56EE5C79.title: "&a飞龙能量模块&f&7[Wyvern Energy Module]&f"
	quest.12469CC0CCFBA1C5.quest_desc: ["最好的剑加上最快的镐再加上铲子？!？!你还想要什么!\\n&7[The best Sword plus the fastest Pickaxe plus the Shovel?!?! What more could you want!]&f"]
	quest.12469CC0CCFBA1C5.title: "混沌法杖&7[Chaotic Staff]&f"
	quest.129E09C03E40BA57.quest_desc: ["&a反应堆&f以&a觉醒龙块&f为燃料,别担心,它很高效!&a燃料转化&f决定了&a觉醒龙块&f何时会转化为混沌.它一次只能容纳8个方块,并且只能在反应堆关闭时添加或补充燃料.SAS模式有助于简化这个过程!另外,燃料放入右下角的槽位.\\n&7[The Reactor takes Awakened Draconium as Fuel, don't worry its efficient! Fuel Conversion determines when the Awakened Draconium will change to Chaos. It can take only 8 BLocks at a time and can only be Fueled or Refueled when the Reactor is shut off. SAS mode helps to make that easier! Also Fuel goes into the bottom right Slots.]&f"]
	quest.129E09C03E40BA57.title: "我们反应堆的燃料&7[Fuel for our Reactor]&f"
	quest.12BDE512C734D19A.quest_desc: ["&a龙核心&f是&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f中许多配方的重要成分.尤其是基础等级的物品.\\n&7[Draconium Cores are a vital Ingredient in many recipes in Draconic Evolution. Especially for Basic Tier items.]&f"]
	quest.12BDE512C734D19A.title: "基础(龙)核心&7[Basic (Draconium) Core]&f"
	quest.131AA933D59D3017.quest_desc: [
		"第5级需要90个&a龙锭&f方块和80个&a红石砖&f,以及4个高级稳定器或36个稳定器.\\n&7[Tier 5 needs 90 Draconium Ingot Blocks and 80 Redstone Blocks, along with 4 Advanced Stabilizers or 36 Stabilizers.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_5off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_5on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.131AA933D59D3017.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f59,300,000,000 RF&7[Stores: 59,300,000,000 RF]&f"
	quest.131AA933D59D3017.title: "第5级&7[Tier 5]&f"
	quest.154D9EA863FD2A32.title: "&a混沌箭矢穿透模块&f&7[Chaotic Projectile Penetration Module]&f"
	quest.164BBBD98163F64C.quest_desc: ["查看模块以了解更多关于如何使用和升级DE物品的信息!它可以制作耕地或拿走你的钱.哦,等等,Minecraft的锄头,抱歉,我想的是另一个.\\n&7[Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! It can make farmland or take your money. Oh wait Minecraft Hoe sorry I was thinking of a different one.]&f"]
	quest.164BBBD98163F64C.title: "&a飞龙锄&f&7[Wyvern Hoe]&f"
	quest.165030137EF59299.title: "飞龙范围效果模块&7[Wyvern Area-Of-Effect Module]&f"
	quest.166D2A191871F80E.quest_desc: ["&a飞龙镐&f的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of the Wyvern Pickaxe.]&f"]
	quest.166D2A191871F80E.title: "&a神龙镐&f&7[Draconic Pickaxe]&f"
	quest.16FF2219F110F50A.quest_desc: ["不朽模块的作用类似于制造它的东西,复苏图腾!当你的生命值降至0时,你不会死亡,模块会激活,给予你伤害吸收和生命恢复效果,拯救你的生命.它有冷却时间,并且需要消耗OP来再次充能.在那段时间内尽量不要死!更好的升级意味着更短的冷却时间.\\n&7[Undying acts as the thing that makes it, the Recovery Totem! When your hearts are down to 0 instead of dying the Module will activate, giving you Absorption and Regeneration, saving your life. It has a Cooldown and needs to use OP to power up again. Try not to die during that time! Better upgrades means less cooldowns.]&f"]
	quest.16FF2219F110F50A.title: "飞龙不朽模块&7[Wyvern Undying Module]&f"
	quest.1830412AB77E9526.quest_desc: ["对于弓这样原始的东西,你不能指望完美的精度.好吧,如果你使用这些模块,你可以.箭矢更有可能击中目标而不会偏离轨道.\\n&7[With something so primitive as a Bow you can't expect perfect Accuracy. Well you can if you use these Modules. The Arrow is much more likely to hit its target and not go off course.]&f"]
	quest.1830412AB77E9526.title: "&a飞龙射击精度模块&f&7[Wyvern Projectile Accuracy Module]&f"
	quest.1A53B6544782442E.quest_desc: ["护盾控制模块会改变你实际拥有的护盾以及护盾的恢复时机.\\n&7[Shield Control changes the actual Shield you have and when it regenerates.]&f"]
	quest.1A53B6544782442E.title: "&a飞龙护盾控制模块&f&7[Wyvern Shield Control Module]&f"
	quest.1C8210712349A2E3.quest_desc: ["前提很简单,斧头和剑可以造成更多&a伤害&f.是的,效果可以叠加!\\n&7[Pretty simple premise, Axes and Swords can do more Damage. Yes, it stacks!]&f"]
	quest.1C8210712349A2E3.title: "基础&a伤害模块&f&7[Basic Damage Module]&f"
	quest.1D3E2363CFD4C5E0.quest_desc: ["&a聚合装置&f有等级,由注入器决定.等级按升序排列:龙(我称之为基础以帮助区分)、飞龙、觉醒龙和混沌.注入器需要放置在&a聚合核心&f的左右两侧,距离它几个方块远.它们可以以十字形放置,核心每侧最多5个.要为它们提供能量,放置连接到它们的继电器输入/输出水晶即可,查看水晶绑定以了解更多信息.\\n&7[Fusion Crafting has Tiers which is determined by the Injectors. The Tiers go in ascending order: Draconium (I refer to it as Basic to help differentiate), Wyvern, Draconic, and Chaotic. The Injectors need to be placed on the Left and Right of the Fusion Crafting Core, a few blocks away from it. They can be placed in a cross shape at a max of 5 on each side of the Crafting Core. To give them Energy putting Relay IO Crystals connected to them will work, check out Crystal Binding to learn more.]&f"]
	quest.1D3E2363CFD4C5E0.title: "基础等级&7[Basic Tier]&f"
	quest.1E41A5071854DEC8.title: "&a飞龙伤害模块&f&7[Wyvern Damage Module]&f"
	quest.1F7D147C9AF6A4FC.quest_desc: [
		"第四级有所不同.首先,它需要26个&a红石砖&f包裹核心.然后在红石上方需要54个&a龙锭&f方块.\\n&7[Tier 4 is different. First, it needs 26 Redstone Blocks encasing the Core. Then above the Redstone it needs 54 Draconium Ingot Blocks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_4off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_4on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.1F7D147C9AF6A4FC.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f9,880,000,000 RF&7[Stores: 9,880,000,000 RF]&f"
	quest.1F7D147C9AF6A4FC.title: "第四级&7[Tier 4]&f"
	quest.20D8DA523E900A52.quest_desc: ["无线&a能量链接&f有助于让无线水晶为你的物品充能.模块越多,它能承受的OP就越多,且速率更佳.\\n&7[Wireless Energy Links help to make it so Wireless Crystals can charge your items. The more modules, the more OP it can take it and at a better rate.]&f"]
	quest.20D8DA523E900A52.title: "无线&a能量链接&f&7[Wireless Energy Link]&f"
	quest.2158A566C2F54AA9.title: "&a神龙护盾控制模块&f&7[Draconic Shield Control Module]&f"
	quest.22D383BAEF8A2B39.quest_desc: ["你知道传说中的Paxel吗？那是镐、斧和锹的结合体？这个也类似,是剑、镐和锹的结合体!它能做所有龙之工具能做的事!\\n&7[You know the legendary Paxel? A combination of Picks, Axes, and Shovels? This is similar, being a combination of Swords, Pickaxes, and Shovels! It does everything the Draconic Tools do!]&f"]
	quest.22D383BAEF8A2B39.title: "龙之权杖&7[Draconic Staff]&f"
	quest.236C936FE3BA8396.title: "&a混沌飞行模块&f&7[Chaotic Flight Module]&f"
	quest.265D0DB0E8CED73B.title: "&a神龙箭矢重力修正模块&f&7[Draconic Projectile Gravity Compensation Module]&f"
	quest.26DF1427AC3966DE.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f,一个非常有趣且强力的模组!要开始,你需要开采龙之矿石来获得&a龙尘&f.它在所有(原版)维度生成,但末地最多!\\n&7[Welcome to Draconic Evolution, a very fun and OP mod! To get started you'll need to mine Draconic Ore to get Draconic Dust. It spawns in all (Vanilla) Dimensions but the most is in the End!]&f"]
	quest.26DF1427AC3966DE.title: "&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f&7[Draconic Evolution]&f"
	quest.285656AF1F870AF8.quest_desc: ["两个基础级灌注之一,但别小看龙之箱子.它比双箱子的空间还大,可以熔炼和合成物品,最棒的是它可以变色!这绝对是我在所有模组中最喜欢的箱子!\\n&7[1 of the 2 Basic Tier Infusions but don't underestimate the Draconic Chest. It holds more space than a double chest, it can smelt and craft items, and best of all it can change colors! Easily my favorite Chest in any mod!]&f"]
	quest.285656AF1F870AF8.title: "&a龙箱&f&7[Draconium Chest]&f"
	quest.28AF8DD34412CBAA.title: "&a神龙速度模块&f&7[Draconic Speed Module]&f"
	quest.295EB6CFEC029AE2.quest_desc: ["在你来到这里之前,首先需要一个内含OP的物品:&a飞龙弓&f、&a混沌通量容器&f、能量权杖等等.然后你需要在物品中放入一个&a能量模块&f,它决定了物品的OP存储容量,这也是物品用来供能的东西.一旦你有了这些,制作并放置&a能量注入器&f,向其中注入OP,然后把你的物品放进去!当其中的OP亮起并移动时,你就知道它在工作了.\\n&7[Before you get here first you need an item that needs OP in it: Wyvern Bow, Chaotic Capacitor, Staff of Power whatever. Then you need an Energy Module in the item, that determines the OP storage in the item and that's what the item will use to power up. Once you have that, make and place the Energy Transfuser, get OP in it, then place your item into it! You'll know it's working when the OP in it lights up and moves.]&f"]
	quest.295EB6CFEC029AE2.title: "为物品添加OP&7[Adding OP to items]&f"
	quest.2A5C5B44E9643A5D.title: "&a混沌速度模块&f&7[Chaotic Speed Module]&f"
	quest.2AA08313F927981E.title: "&a飞龙速度模块&f&7[Wyvern Speed Module]&f"
	quest.2AAE61752728EA8D.quest_desc: ["当”下落”时,你的挖掘速度会变慢.这包括创造模式飞行甚至在水里弹跳时.幸好你可以使用&a空中速掘&f附魔来抵消它!这不是原版附魔,但仍然很有用!哦等等,我本来应该讲模块的……道理一样!\\n&7[When 'falling' your Mining is slowed down. That includes when creative flying or even bouncing in water. Thankfully you can use Air Affinity Enchantment to negate that! Not a vanilla Enchantment but still helpful! Oh wait I was supposed to talk about the Module... same thing!]&f"]
	quest.2AAE61752728EA8D.title: "&a挖掘稳定器&f Module&7[Mining Stabilizer Module]&f"
	quest.2B6D71DAF72EAFA4.quest_desc: ["&a电容&f充当&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f的电池.它们需要&a能量模块&f来实际储存能量,记住,”多多益善!”.\\n&7[The Capacitors act as the Batteries for Draconic Evolution. They need Energy Modules to actually hold Energy and remember, 'The more the merrier!'.]&f"]
	quest.2B6D71DAF72EAFA4.title: "&a飞龙通量容器&f&7[Wyvern Capacitor]&f"
	quest.2D9AF97C03C5AEC7.quest_desc: ["对于第5-8级,你需要高级稳定器.什么是高级稳定器？它是9个稳定器,全部放在一个3x1x3的区域内.当正确制作时,它会变成一个圆形!就像你制作单个稳定器那样做就行.\\n&7[For Tier 5-8 you'll need Advanced Stabilizers. What's an Advanced Stabilizer? It's 9 Stabilizers all in a 3x1x3 Area. When made right it'll transform into a circle! Just do that same way you'd do 1 Stabilizer.]&f"]
	quest.2D9AF97C03C5AEC7.title: "高级稳定器&7[Advanced Stabilizers]&f"
	quest.2DB2A4A1182FE0BB.quest_desc: [
		"第六级需要150个&a龙锭&f方块和178个&a红石砖&f(别忘了36个稳定器).\\n&7[Tier 6 needs 150 Draconium Ingot Blocks and 178 Redstone Blocks (Don't forget 36 Stabilizers).]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_6off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_6on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.2DB2A4A1182FE0BB.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f356,000,000,000 RF&7[Stores: 356,000,000,000 RF]&f"
	quest.2DB2A4A1182FE0BB.title: "第六级&7[Tier 6]&f"
	quest.2E74B5149D4BD0A0.quest_desc: ["基础(&a能量中继器&f)水晶是开始用&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f传输能量的起点!\\n&7[Basic (Energy Relay) Crystal is the start to moving Energy with Draconic Evolution! ]&f"]
	quest.2E74B5149D4BD0A0.title: "基础&a能量中继器&f水晶&7[Basic Energy Relay Crystal]&f"
	quest.30F97EB743B0A07F.quest_desc: ["查看模块以了解更多关于如何使用和升级DE物品的信息!&a飞龙&f斧类似于战斗更新后的Minecraft斧头.它们可以设计成斩杀敌人的武器,也可以设计成砍伐树木的工具.\\n&7[Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! The Wyvern Axe is similar to Minecraft Axes after Combat Updates. They can designed off a weapon to slay foes, or a tool to chop down trees.]&f"]
	quest.30F97EB743B0A07F.title: "&a飞龙斧&f&7[Wyvern Axe]&f"
	quest.3235FBD9CE21D5EE.quest_desc: ["查看模块以了解更多关于如何使用和升级DE物品的信息!我知道你们玩家真正关心的是&a飞龙锹&f.你不再需要度过不眠之夜了,因为现在你知道,DE锹可以开辟道路.\\n&7[Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! I know what you fellow Player really care about the Wyvern Shovel. You don't need to spend anymore sleepless nights because now you know, the DE Shovels can make pathways.]&f"]
	quest.3235FBD9CE21D5EE.title: "&a飞龙锹&f&7[Wyvern Shovel]&f"
	quest.32EBB3D53AA91E09.quest_desc: ["除非你是使用&a夜视&f材质包的小作弊者,否则你可能会觉得黑暗有点令人担忧.幸好DE胸甲中的&a夜视模块&f有助于克服在黑暗中看不见的恐惧.不过,不是对黑暗中的东西的恐惧……\\n&7[Unless you're a little cheater who uses Night Vision Texture Packs, you might find the dark a little worry some. Thankfully Night Vision Module in a DE Chestplate helps get over the fear of not being able to see in the dark. Not the fear of what's in the dark though...]&f"]
	quest.32EBB3D53AA91E09.title: "&a夜视模块&f&7[Night Vision Module]&f"
	quest.33D2901594655A77.title: "混沌范围效果模块&7[Chaotic Area-Of-Effect Module]&f"
	quest.34D3F6D54F5B26C2.quest_desc: ["一把升级的锄头,所以会变成一位优雅美丽的女士？\\n&7[An upgraded hoe, so would just be a fine and nice lady?]&f"]
	quest.34D3F6D54F5B26C2.title: "&a神龙锄&f&7[Draconic Hoe]&f"
	quest.35767977FB9E0B1B.quest_desc: [
		"第二级需要6个&a龙锭&f方块,核心每边一个.然后,显然还需要制作4个稳定器.\\n&7[Tier 2 needs 6 Draconium Ingot Blocks, 1 on each side of the Core. Then, obviously the 4 Stabilizers to be made.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_2off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_2on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.35767977FB9E0B1B.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f273,000,000 RF&7[Stores: 273,000,000 RF]&f"
	quest.35767977FB9E0B1B.title: "第二级&7[Tier 2]&f"
	quest.35A674E2C6F66673.title: "&a混沌箭矢精度模块&f&7[Chaotic Projectile Accuracy Module]&f"
	quest.366431661CC43A6E.quest_desc: [
		"此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.]&f"
		"由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&e保留所有权利&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非该团队发布的公开整合包.\\n&7[As all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by the AllTheMods Team, without explicit permission.]&f"
		""
		""
		""
		"此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"
	]
	quest.36DAFC3FECC67406.quest_desc: ["DE能提供的最佳能量电池.\\n&7[Best Energy Battery DE will give.]&f"]
	quest.36DAFC3FECC67406.title: "&a混沌通量容器&f&7[Chaotic Capacitor]&f"
	quest.36F123B2A6B52A01.quest_desc: ["这些可以传输更多能量并拥有更多链接.这是最高等级的能量水晶.\\n&7[These can move more Energy and have more links. The highest level Energy Crystals go.]&f"]
	quest.36F123B2A6B52A01.title: "&a神龙能量中继水晶&f&7[Draconic Energy Relay Crystal]&f"
	quest.3765485408041FC6.quest_desc: ["查看模块以了解更多关于如何使用和升级DE物品的信息!镐作为普通的第六级镐工作.它们可以挖掘所有等级的方块,从石头到不可得矿.挖掘的物品将自动进入你的物品栏.\\n&7[Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! Pickaxes work as a normal Tier 6 Pickaxe. They can mine every level of block, from Stone to 难得素. Items mined will automatically go to your Inventory.]&f"]
	quest.3765485408041FC6.title: "&a飞龙镐&f&7[Wyvern Pickaxe]&f"
	quest.376D154F27A00BCD.quest_desc: ["物理和DE以及背叛它们是怎么回事？重力会随着箭射出时间将其向下拉.重力补偿让我们少担心这一点.\\n&7[What is up with Physics and De and betraying them? Gravity pulls the Arrow down over the time it's shot. Gravity Compensation makes us worry less about that.]&f"]
	quest.376D154F27A00BCD.title: "&a飞龙箭矢减少模块&f&7[Wyvern Projectile Gravity Compensation Module]&f"
	quest.37CC51B689CB8A40.quest_desc: ["胸甲的工作方式类似于Meka套装.任何本应对你造成的伤害都会被抵消,并从你的护盾中扣除.护盾容量是你能持有的护盾量,充能速率是它填充的速度,而充能时会消耗OP.\\n&7[Chestplates work similar to the Meka-Suit. Any damage that would be dealt to you is negated and instead taken off your Shield. Shield capacity is how much Shield you can hold, recharge rate is how fast it fills up, and OP will be used when recharging.]&f"]
	quest.37CC51B689CB8A40.title: "&a飞龙护盾容量模块&f&7[Wyvern Shield Capacity Module]&f"
	quest.389655CD41C7A691.quest_desc: [
		"第一级只需要核心和4个要制作的稳定器.\\n&7[Tier 1 only needs the Core and 4 Stabilizers to be made.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_1off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_1on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.389655CD41C7A691.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f45,500,000 RF&7[Stores: 45,500,000 RF]&f"
	quest.389655CD41C7A691.title: "第一级&7[Tier 1]&f"
	quest.38AD547C36BDF4C4.title: "&a神龙箭矢精度模块&f&7[Draconic Projectile Accuracy Module]&f"
	quest.39865681B03CABAA.quest_desc: ["水有点粘稠,或者至少比空气密度大.因此,水下挖掘速度较慢.你可以使用&a水亲和模块&f的附魔,或者使用这个模块.随你选择!\\n&7[Water is a little viscous, or atleast more dense than air. Because of that Mining Underwater is slower. You can use the Enchantment of Aqua Affinity, or use this Module. Your choice!]&f"]
	quest.39865681B03CABAA.title: "水适应模块&7[Aqua Adapt Module]&f"
	quest.39AF9B1A996DA949.quest_desc: ["它就像&a下界合金剑&f,但更好更酷!\\n&7[It's like the Netherite Sword but much better and much cooler!]&f"]
	quest.39AF9B1A996DA949.title: "&a混沌剑&f&7[Chaotic Sword]&f"
	quest.3B4CEE8A8CE0D6CB.quest_desc: [
		"快到了!第七级.210个&a龙锭&f和328个&a红石砖&f!\\n&7[Almost there! Tier 7. 210 Draconium Ingots and 328 Redstone Blocks!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_7off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_7on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.3B4CEE8A8CE0D6CB.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f2,140,000,000,000 RF&7[Stores: 2,140,000,000,000 RF]&f"
	quest.3B4CEE8A8CE0D6CB.title: "第七级&7[Tier 7]&f"
	quest.3BE3B54B4A681668.quest_desc: ["这就是关键所在,你喜欢像卡车一样伤害敌人但速度慢得多吗？还是你宁愿做一个使用剑的普通人.\\n&7[This is where it comes down to, do you like to hurt your enemies like a Truck but much slower? Or would you rather be a normal person who uses a Sword.]&f"]
	quest.3BE3B54B4A681668.title: "&a混沌斧&f&7[Chaotic Axe]&f"
	quest.3CB8F5F1D33C8F9F.quest_desc: ["和上一个任务一样,只是更多,多得多.\\n&7[Same as the previous quest, just more, a lot more.]&f"]
	quest.3CB8F5F1D33C8F9F.title: "&a飞龙大护盾容量模块&f&7[Wyvern Large Shield Capacity Module]&f"
	quest.3DF794EBCAA7AE1A.title: "龙之&a树木砍伐&f器&7[Draconic Tree Harvester]&f"
	quest.3FD19A001899D8C6.quest_desc: ["好的,这个既能滑翔又能真正飞行,更准确地说,是创造模式飞行.\\n&7[Okay now this ones give both Gliding and actual Flying, Creative Flight to be more exact.]&f"]
	quest.3FD19A001899D8C6.title: "&a神龙飞行模块&f&7[Draconic Flight Module]&f"
	quest.40F34EBE09DA7752.quest_desc: ["自动进食会在你饥饿时自动喂食你物品栏中的任何食物.不过它有最大食物点数存储,每个完整的饥饿条是2个食物点数.所以基础版只能存储相当于8块牛排的量.\\n&7[Auto-Feed will automatically feed you any food in your Inventory when hungry. It has a max Food Point storage though, each full bar is 2 Food Points. So the Basic one can only hold 8 Steaks worth.]&f"]
	quest.40F34EBE09DA7752.title: "Basic &a自动进食模块&f&7[Basic Auto Feed Module]&f"
	quest.41BD497108CA109F.quest_desc: ["&a觉醒龙&f来自&a聚合装置&f方块.这些方块可以拆解成9个锭.这些是&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f中第二重要的锭,对于飞龙和龙之等级非常必要.\\n&7[Awakened Draconium comes from Fusion Crafting the blocks. The blocks can be uncrafted into 9 Ingots. These are the second most important Ingots in Draconic Evolution and very necessary for the Wyvern and Draconic Tiers.]&f"]
	quest.41BD497108CA109F.title: "&a觉醒龙&f&7[Awakened Draconium]&f"
	quest.421954D7D46FAAD6.quest_desc: ["&a能量核心稳定器&f……稳定？核心.对于前4级核心,你只需要在其周围放置4个稳定器.你也可以通过稳定器访问核心的GUI.如果它们放置得离核心太近或在错误的位置,它会告诉你这是不正确的.\\n&7[Energy Core Stabilizers... stabilize? The Core. For the first 4 Tiers of Cores you need only 4 Stabilizers around it. You can access the GUi of the Core through the Stabilizers as well. If they are placed too close to the Core or in the wrong spots it will tell you it's incorrect.]&f"]
	quest.421954D7D46FAAD6.title: "&a能量核心稳定器&f&7[Energy Core Stabilizers]&f"
	quest.43C2B07AB25C708E.quest_desc: ["&a飞龙弓&f的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of the Wyvern Bow.]&f"]
	quest.43C2B07AB25C708E.title: "&a神龙弓&f&7[Draconic Bow]&f"
	quest.45EE60207C466D6C.quest_desc: ["要进入&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f,你需要&a混沌碎片&f.&a混沌碎片&f位于末地的混沌岛上,由&a混沌守卫&f守护.前往末地,X/Z坐标为10k的倍数.10k, 10k / 10k, 20k / 20k, 20k 等等.\\n&7[To get into Draconic Evolution you'll need Chaos Shards. Chaos Shards are in Chaos Islands guarded by Chaos Guardians in the End. Go to the End at an X/Z coordinate that is a multiple of 10k. 10k, 10k / 10k, 20k / 20k, 20k etc.]&f"]
	quest.45EE60207C466D6C.quest_subtitle: "寻找混沌岛&7[Finding Chaos Island]&f"
	quest.45EE60207C466D6C.title: "他在哪里？&7[Where is he?]&f"
	quest.4638F21544D6D337.title: "&a混沌纠缠量子能量隧道模块&f&7[Chaos-Entangled Quantum Energy Tunnel]&f"
	quest.46C816844C513D5D.quest_desc: ["&a飞龙锹&f的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of the Wyvern Shovel.]&f"]
	quest.46C816844C513D5D.title: "&a神龙锹&f&7[Draconic Shovel]&f"
	quest.4903BDC389C73082.title: "&a神龙箭矢伤害模块&f&7[Draconic Projectile Damage Module]&f"
	quest.4A3A5684302C8627.title: "&a混沌护盾容量模块&f&7[Chaotic Shield Capacity Module]&f"
	quest.4AAADEC52D16461A.quest_desc: ["基本上它开启了自动跳跃.我个人喜欢它,但用不用取决于你!\\n&7[Basically it turns auto-jump on. Personally I like it but it's up to you to use it!]&f"]
	quest.4AAADEC52D16461A.title: "&a攀爬模块&f&7[Hill Step Module]&f"
	quest.4AB564420C48579B.quest_desc: ["&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f认为,当你可以使用带有内置护盾的单个胸甲时,没有必要用可怜的盔甲覆盖全身.等等,它们不是内置的,你需要模块……抱歉.\\n&7[Draconic Evolution doesn't see the need for covering the whole body in pathetic armor when you can use a single Chestplate with built in shields. Wait, they aren't built in you need Modules for them... sorry.]&f"]
	quest.4AB564420C48579B.title: "&a双足飞龙胸甲&f&7[Wyvern Chestplate]&f"
	quest.4ABEF61DADBD0640.quest_desc: ["大多数弓是半自动的.你必须拉弦、释放、再放一支箭,然后重复.相反,跳过所有这些,让弓在每次拉满时自动发射.只需按住&a右键&f,看着它发射!\\n&7[Most Bows are Semi-Automatic. You have to draw the string, release, and put another Arrow in the bow, and repeat. Instead skip all that let the Bow automatically fire everytime it's fully drawn. Just hold Right Click and watch it go!]&f"]
	quest.4ABEF61DADBD0640.title: "&a自动射击模块&f&7[Auto Fire Module]&f"
	quest.4B7840F1A8CF1378.quest_desc: ["&a聚合装置&f是制作大多数(至少是有趣的物品)的方式.要开始,你需要一个&a聚合核心&f,将其放置在地面大约一格高的位置.核心是配方可以从JEI自动放置的地方,中间物品放置的地方,以及最终物品将被放置的地方.它需要注入器放置在离它几格远的地方,面向核心的两侧.查看下一个任务以了解更多关于这些的信息.注入器还需要能量,这将在水晶绑定任务中进一步解释.\\n&7[Fusion Crafting is how most (atleast the fun items) will be made. To get started you need a Fusion Crafting Core, place it down about a block above the ground. The Core is where recipes can be autoplaced in from JEI, where the middle item goes, and where the end item will be put. It will need the Injectors put a few blocks away from it looking toward the Core on two sides of it. Check next Quest to find more on those. The Injectors will also need Energy which will be explained more in the Crystal Binding Quest.]&f"]
	quest.4B7840F1A8CF1378.title: "&a聚合装置&f&7[Fusion Crafting]&f"
	quest.4B9FF9E972B0E530.quest_desc: ["&a能量链接&f或隧道越好,显然它能传输的OP就越多,但你可能也注意到了&a能量链接&f缺少的东西.它不能在维度间工作!幸好更好的可以,只需确保另一边区块已加载.\\n&7[The better the Energy Link or Tunnel obviously the more OP it can transfer, but also you might have noticed something missing with the Energy Link. It doesn't work between Dimensions! Thankfully the better ones can, just make sure the other side is chunkloaded.]&f"]
	quest.4B9FF9E972B0E530.title: "&a量子能量隧道模块&f&7[Quantum Energy Tunnel]&f"
	quest.4CD2ADD3601B8191.quest_desc: ["想让你的护盾恢复,而不是在你快死的时候才恢复？那么,你需要恢复模块.模块越多,恢复越快.\\n&7[Want your Shield to come back and not just when you almost die? Then, you'll need Recovery Modules. The more Modules the faster it recovers.]&f"]
	quest.4CD2ADD3601B8191.title: "&a飞龙护盾恢复模块&f&7[Wyvern Shield Recovery Module]&f"
	quest.4E27182763DA83DC.quest_desc: ["&a双足飞龙胸甲&f的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of the Wyvern Chestplate.]&f"]
	quest.4E27182763DA83DC.title: "&a神龙胸甲&f&7[Draconic Chestplate]&f"
	quest.4EFFE300EC781C3E.quest_desc: ["模块对我们的DE物品非常重要.重要到没有它们就无法工作!大多数模块由&a模块核心&f或前一个模块制成.手持物品并按Shift和C打开&a模式菜单&f.在那里你会看到一些插槽和按钮!插槽是模块实际放置的地方,网格决定了可以放置多少个模块.当一个模块显示1x1时,它只占用1个插槽,而显示2x2的将占用4个插槽.右侧最下面的按钮会显示可以应用于你手持物品的模块.其余的只是改变GUI的外观.\\n&7[Modules are very important to our DE items. So important they don't work without them! Most Modules are made from a Module Core or a previous Module. Hold an item and press Shift and C to open the Module Menu. There you'll see some slots and buttons! The Slots are where Modules will actually go and the Grid is what determines how many Modules can go. When a Module says 1x1 it'll only take 1 Slot, while one that says 2z2 will take uo 4 slots. The lowest button on the right will show what Modules can be applied to the Item you are holding. The rest just change the look of GUI.]&f"]
	quest.4EFFE300EC781C3E.title: "模块!&7[Modules!]&f"
	quest.4F6A9F1AEFD535F5.title: "&a神龙大护盾容量模块&f&7[Draconic Large Shield Capacity Module]&f"
	quest.50013DD7370F8EDB.title: "&a混沌跳跃模块&f&7[Chaotic Jump Module]&f"
	quest.5021D159A5EC2315.title: "&a神龙能量模块&f&7[Draconic Energy Module]&f"
	quest.51CF09EC333DB1A3.quest_desc: ["为了在&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f的&a聚合装置&f中升级,配方所需的注入器必须至少是该等级或更高.例如,如果你想制作&a飞龙斧&f,你至少需要6个飞龙注入器,每边3个.别担心,合成核心保持不变!\\n&7[In order to Tier up in Draconic Evolution Fusion Crafting, the needed Injectors for a recipe must be atleast the Tier or higher. Like if you want to make the Wyvern Axe you need atleast 6 Wyvern Injectors, with 3 on each sides. Don't worry the Crafting Core stays the same!]&f"]
	quest.51CF09EC333DB1A3.title: "飞龙等级&7[Wyvern Tier]&f"
	quest.529123A789D790E3.title: "&a飞龙跳跃模块&f&7[Wyvern Jump Module]&f"
	quest.52C301DF1776E0D8.title: "&a混沌箭矢伤害模块&f&7[Chaotic Projectile Damage Module]&f"
	quest.52C3F61D678B00F5.quest_desc: ["一把&a混沌锄&f,我以前和其中一个约会过.\\n&7[A Chaotic Hoe, I dated one of those while back.]&f"]
	quest.52C3F61D678B00F5.title: "&a混沌锄&f&7[Chaotic Hoe]&f"
	quest.52EA9793A7100E75.title: "混沌不朽模块&7[Chaotic Undying Module]&f"
	quest.542AD6FD1927C3E6.title: "龙之不朽模块&7[Draconic Undying Module]&f"
	quest.5443E15E226DFC86.quest_desc: ["能量塔是你将OP输入和输出&a能量核心&f的方式.将它们至少放置在靠近核心的地方,2个塔,一个用于输入,一个用于输出(你可以使用更多).然后,在它们上面放置玻璃,它们将自动组装并瞄准最近的&a能量核心&f.&a右键&f点击塔上新形成的球体,以更改它们是输入还是输出(你可以从箭头和设计上看出来).然后,你可以将水晶连接到它们以传输OP进出!\\n&7[Pylons are how you get OP in and out of the Energy Core. Place them atleast close to the Core, 2 of them 1 for input and 1 for output (you can use more). Then, place Glass over them and they will be assembled automatically targeting the closest Energy Core. Right Click the newly formed balls ontop of the Pylons to change whether they are Input or Output (you'll know from the arrows and design of them). Then, you can attach Crystals to them to move OP in and out!]&f"]
	quest.5443E15E226DFC86.title: "能量通过这些进出&7[Power comes and goes through these]&f"
	quest.54F78C9A945CF0E7.title: "&a混沌能量模块&f&7[Chaotic Energy Module]&f"
	quest.574E5806D1A98FE5.quest_desc: ["&a能量模块&f是最重要的模块,使用DE物品时需要它们.其中的数量决定了物品可以持有和接收的OP量,查看&a能量注入器&f以了解更多关于充能的信息.&a能量模块&f的等级越高,物品可以持有和使用的OP就越多.这很重要,因为当物品升级时,每次使用会消耗更多OP.\\n&7[Energy Modules are the most important Modules and are needed for using DE items. The amount in them determines how much OP an item can hold and take in, check out the Energy Infuser to learn more about charging. The later the Tier of Energy Module the more OP items can hold and use. This is important as when items are upgraded they use more OP per use.]&f"]
	quest.574E5806D1A98FE5.title: "基础&a能量模块&f&7[Basic Energy Module]&f"
	quest.5895B7FA5497BD68.quest_desc: ["&a飞龙斧&f的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of the Wyvern Axe.]&f"]
	quest.5895B7FA5497BD68.title: "&a神龙斧&f&7[Draconic Axe]&f"
	quest.594BBD31461F212D.title: "&a神龙护盾恢复模块&f&7[Draconic Shield Recovery Module]&f"
	quest.5ADFC45B03BAB852.quest_desc: ["这就是&a龙芯&f的用途.\\n&7[This is what Draconic Cores are for.]&f"]
	quest.5ADFC45B03BAB852.title: "龙之等级&7[Draconic Tier]&f"
	quest.5BC6CC3C09F512A7.quest_desc: [
		"The Reactor Core is the most important part of the Reactor, IE the Core! Place it 5 blocks or more from the Injector and Stabilizers, and you can right click it to see it's GUI here you'll find a few bars, a ball, buttons, and slots. The Bars go from left to right: Heat, Containment Field, Energy Saturation, and Fuel Conversion. You already learned about the Field and Energy and you will learn about the Fuel in a next quest. So the Heat is pretty important as when warming up it will raise to 2000C before being ready to activate. Make sure it doesn't get too high or else... meltdown! The Ball is the image of your Core, right now I have a bug where the Core doesn't have a texture so I can't explain much. The Buttons change the appearance of GUI, to activate or shutdown the Reactor, and charge it."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_reactor_off_down.png width:200 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_reactor_off_up.png width:150 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.5BC6CC3C09F512A7.quest_subtitle: "无限能量&7[UNLIMITED POWER]&f"
	quest.5BC6CC3C09F512A7.title: "建造反应堆&7[Building the Reactor]&f"
	quest.5C2CF51D28F84CBE.quest_desc: [
		"Now the actual fight starts, he has two health bars both need to get taken to 0 to get the Chaos Shards. Don't get too close or he'll hit you with a barrage of Fireballs! {BTW in older versions the Chaos Guardian could even kill someone in Creative mode! Fortunately it can't anymore)"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_guardian.png width:150 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.5C2CF51D28F84CBE.title: "击杀&a混沌守卫&f&7[Kill the Chaos Guardian]&f"
	quest.5D87088E8D71DB9B.quest_desc: ["输入/输出水晶作为可以相互连接并传输能量的方块.要链接它们,请按住Shift键&a右击&f使用水晶绑定器设置一个水晶,然后&a右击&f你想要连接的任意水晶.当你查看水晶时,它会显示”从方块输入”或”输出到方块”.输入是你想要从中获取OP(操作潜能)的地方,输出是你想要OP传输到的地方.\\n&7[The IO Crystals work as blocks that can connect to each other and move power from one another. To link them Shift Right Click with a Crystal Binder to set one and then right click whichever Crystal you want connected. When you look at the Crystal it will say either Input from block or Output to block. Input is the one you want to take OP from and Output to where you want it to go.]&f"]
	quest.5D87088E8D71DB9B.title: "移动OP&7[Moving OP]&f"
	quest.5E0D78B7B2CF1729.quest_desc: ["我知道这是飞龙等级,但为什么这里会出现龙之研究的物品？\\n&7[I know it's Wyvern Tier so why is a Draconic item in here?]&f"]
	quest.5E0D78B7B2CF1729.title: "&a龙芯&f&7[Draconic Core]&f"
	quest.5E671F1F370DDE43.title: "&a神龙自动进食模块&f&7[Draconic Auto Feed Module]&f"
	quest.5E8D527DE9D7DD46.quest_desc: ["在你的胸甲上装备这个,你就可以滑翔了!就像使用鞘翅一样(但不会占用护甲槽).我不喜欢称之为飞行,更像是”有型地下坠”.\\n&7[With this on your Chestplate you can Glide! As if you were using an Elytra (But without cost of Armor). I don't like to call it flying, rather 'falling with style'.]&f"]
	quest.5E8D527DE9D7DD46.title: "&a飞龙飞行模块&f&7[Wyvern Flight Module]&f"
	quest.607337D8AA20FA18.quest_desc: ["所有与被砍伐树木相连的树木,都会一并倒下.\\n&7[All Trees attached to whats chopped down, comes with it.]&f"]
	quest.607337D8AA20FA18.title: "&a飞龙树木砍伐者&f&7[Wyvern Tree Harvester]&f"
	quest.60C27206F1414DD6.quest_desc: ["感谢牛顿,我们知道每个作用力都有一个大小相等、方向相反的反作用力.基本上,当箭矢击中生物时,生物的反作用力会施加在箭矢上,使其减速.除非你拥有这个模块.它的作用不是让每个生物都像纸一样脆弱,而是让每个生物都不构成障碍.箭矢在穿透目标后不会减速.\\n&7[Thanks to Newton we know for every action there is an equal and opposite reaction. Basically when an Arrow hits a mob the force of the Mob applies to the Arrow which will slow it down. Unless you have this Module. It doesn't act as if every mob was paper, it acts as if every mob isn't in the way. Arrows won't slow down after Piercing a target.]&f"]
	quest.60C27206F1414DD6.title: "&a神龙反箭矢免疫模块&f&7[Projectile Immunity Cancellation Module]&f"
	quest.61419D230687CBB5.quest_desc: ["速度是物体在特定方向上的速率.既然我们的箭矢不是来自《银河护卫队》,那基本上就是指箭矢的速率.每升一级,箭矢从弓飞到目标所需的时间就会减少.代价是略微降低精准度.\\n&7[Velocity is the speed of an item at a certain direction. Since our Arrow aren't from Guardians of the Galaxy it basically just means the Speed of an Arrow. With each upgrade it takes less time from the Arrow to go from your Bow to your Target. Comes at a cost of a little inaccuracy.]&f"]
	quest.61419D230687CBB5.title: "&a飞龙箭矢速度模块&f&7[Wyvern Projectile Velocity Module]&f"
	quest.655BE42CD5BB9D82.title: "龙之研究范围效果模块&7[Draconic Area-Of-Effect Module]&f"
	quest.6601ACCDDF6CA5FF.quest_desc: ["&a反应堆&f最多只能储存10亿OP,虽然这看起来是个很大的数字,但很快就不够用了.当&a能量储量&f达到100%%时,热量会急剧增加,可能导致熔毁.激活需要500,000,000 OP,而&a能量阀门&f有助于限制OP的输入和输出量.(顺便说一下,1 RF = 1 OP)它们需要红石信号来激活,既可以用于添加OP,也可以用于取出OP.你需要输出能量以避免熔毁,试着把它放进&a能量核心&f里吧!\\n&7[The Reactor can only hold 1 Billion OP and while that may seem like a far number, it won't be for long. When Energy Saturation reaches 100%% it will increase Heat a ton which can lead to Meltdown. It will need 500,000,000 OP to activate and a Flux Gate will help limit how much OP comes in and out. (BTW 1 RF = 1 OP) They need Redstone to activate and can be used for both adding OP and taking out OP. You'll need Energy out to not Meltdown, try putting it in an Energy Core!]&f"]
	quest.6601ACCDDF6CA5FF.title: "启动助力&7[A jump start]&f"
	quest.6616A62426ED4D15.quest_desc: ["注入器需要位于所有稳定器的另一侧,并且必须与核心共享同一轴线.这是OP需要被泵入的地方!要激活并产生OP,需要稍微提高&a能量储量&f.&a能量储量&f是储存的能量,也是即将产生的能量.\\n&7[The Injector needs to be on a different side of all the Stabilizers and has to share the same Axis as the Core. This is where OP will need to pumped in from! To activate and make OP the Energy Saturation needs to be raised up a bit. Energy Saturation is the stored Energy and soon to be made Energy.]&f"]
	quest.6616A62426ED4D15.title: "&a反应堆能量注入器&f&7[Reactor Energy Injector]&f"
	quest.69396F87A09FBD85.quest_desc: ["所有镐子都拥有相同的挖掘等级,所以升级的唯一需求就是更快地挖掘和获得法杖.\\n&7[All Pickaxes mine at the same Mining Tier so the only need to upgrade is to be faster and get the Staffs.]&f"]
	quest.69396F87A09FBD85.title: "&a混沌镐&f&7[Chaotic Pickaxe]&f"
	quest.69986817D58AC8BE.quest_desc: ["稳定器构成了&a容纳力场&f(围绕&a反应堆芯&f的力场护盾).一旦容纳护盾在反应堆开启时降至0,就会开始熔毁.所有4个稳定器都需要距离核心几格远(5格或更多),并且需要与核心大致在同一轴线上才能工作.这些也是你从反应堆输出OP的地方,只是别输出太多!\\n&7[Stabilizers are what form the Containment Field (Force Shield around the Reactor Core). Once Containment Shield is down to 0 while Reactor is turned on it will begin a Meltdown. All 4 Stabilizers need to be a few blocks away (5 or more) from the Core and need to be around same Axis as the Core to work. These are also where you will pipe out OP from the Reactor, just not too much!]&f"]
	quest.69986817D58AC8BE.title: "&a反应堆稳定器&f&7[Reactor Stabilizers]&f"
	quest.6B0CD6732BE0E819.quest_desc: ["其实就是&a跳跃提升&f.\\n&7[Legit just Jump Boost.]&f"]
	quest.6B0CD6732BE0E819.title: "Basic &a指向传送模块&f&7[Basic Jump Module]&f"
	quest.6B8F2E05429C185F.quest_desc: [
		"一旦击败他,他会掉落经验值、一个&a龙之心&f,最重要的是释放&a混沌碎片&f.观察闪电将要击中的地方,然后挖掘其下方.在那里你会找到&a混沌碎片&f.挖掘它可以获得5个&a混沌碎片&f,这些碎片可以合成为更小的部分!\\n&7[Once defeated he'll drop EXP, a Dragon Heart, and most importantly free the Chaos Shards. Look to where Lightning will strike then mine below it. There you will find the Chaos Shard. Mine it to be granted 5 Chaos Shards which can be crafted into smaller parts of it!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_shard.png width:150 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.6B8F2E05429C185F.title: "Chaos Shard{s}"
	quest.6DBD81BA83B1D0A5.quest_desc: ["更多的操作潜能!\\n&7[Even more Operation Potential!]&f"]
	quest.6DBD81BA83B1D0A5.title: "&a神龙通量容器&f&7[Draconic Capacitor]&f"
	quest.7081E9BF44EFBCB0.title: "&a混沌大护盾容量模块&f&7[Chaotic Large Shield Capacity Module]&f"
	quest.710C7FEFAA6C0979.quest_desc: ["&a飞龙剑&f的&a增强&f版本.\\n&7[Upgraded version of the Wyvern Sword.]&f"]
	quest.710C7FEFAA6C0979.title: "&a神龙剑&f&7[Draconic Sword]&f"
	quest.713D3B3954E58C4A.quest_desc: [
		"第3级需要在其周围放置26个&a龙锭&f方块,完全包裹核心,才能制成.\\n&7[Tier 3 needs 26 Draconium Ingot Blocks around it, fully encasing the Core, to be made.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_3off.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_core_3on.png width:100 height:100 align:1}"
	]
	quest.713D3B3954E58C4A.quest_subtitle: "&a储量&f1,640,000,000 RF&7[Stores: 1,640,000,000 RF]&f"
	quest.713D3B3954E58C4A.title: "第3级&7[Tier 3]&f"
	quest.7143CE930D08F160.quest_desc: ["&a作用面积&f是大多数玩家都熟悉的术语.基本上,它会升级工具的工作区域.拥有3x3作用面积的镐子会在3x3区域内挖掘.拥有3x3作用面积的剑会击杀该区域内击中的所有生物.升级越好,区域越大.不,它不能叠加!\\n&7[Area of Effect is a phrase most Gamers would know. Basically it upgrades the working area of the Tool it's on. Pickaxes with 3x3 AOE will mine in a 3x3 area. Swords with 3x3 AOE will kill all mobs hit within that area. The better the upgrade the bigger the area. No, it's not stackable!]&f"]
	quest.7143CE930D08F160.title: "基础范围效果模块&7[Basic Area-Of-Effect Module]&f"
	quest.715F9F7107374299.quest_desc: ["飞龙(&a能量中继器&f)水晶.功能与基础水晶完全相同,只是能量更多,链接也更多.\\n&7[Wyvern (Energy Relay) Crystal. Does exact same as the Basic Crystal just more Energy and more Links.]&f"]
	quest.715F9F7107374299.title: "&a飞龙能量中继水晶&f&7[Wyvern Energy Relay Crystal]&f"
	quest.731A70C25C2C7281.quest_desc: ["从这个工具上获得的物品会进入你的&a末影箱&f.指的是Minecraft原版的末影箱,不是模组添加的.\\n&7[Items gotten from the Tool this is on will go to your Ender Chest. The Minecraft one not modded one.]&f"]
	quest.731A70C25C2C7281.title: "&a末影收集模块&f&7[Ender Collection Module]&f"
	quest.7496B2380A23FDC6.title: "混沌&a树木砍伐&f者&7[Chaotic Tree Harvester]&f"
	quest.74C715F8F24B8BAE.quest_desc: ["功能相同,但增加了过滤选项.\\n&7[Same deal but with options of filtering.]&f"]
	quest.74C715F8F24B8BAE.title: "&a末影收集过滤模块&f&7[Filterable Ender Collection Module]&f"
	quest.75F0405FFAB9C080.quest_desc: ["这将用于最后的等级——混沌等级.希望你已经完成了讲解如何获取&a混沌碎片&f的任务分支!\\n&7[This will be needed for the last Tier, Chaotic Tier. Hopefully you followed the branch of quests that explain how to get Chaos Shards!]&f"]
	quest.75F0405FFAB9C080.title: "&a混沌核心&f&7[Chaotic Core]&f"
	quest.76064465104B1C28.title: "&a神龙护盾容量模块&f&7[Draconic Shield Capacity Module]&f"
	quest.763EB5C911D7E78C.quest_desc: ["注魔合成的终点,混沌等级.一旦达到这个等级,你可以创造一切.不仅是工具,还有反应堆所需的所有物品.\\n&7[End of the road for Crafting Infusions, Chaotic Tier. Everything can be created once you are here. Not just the Tools but also everything you'll need for the Reactor.]&f"]
	quest.763EB5C911D7E78C.title: "混沌等级&7[Chaotic Tier]&f"
	quest.78FBB0C88182040E.quest_desc: ["如果你自1.13版本以来就没玩过Minecraft,这可能会让你困惑,但你知道弩和穿透.它们有一个附魔,可以让箭矢穿过多个目标并持续造成伤害.这个模块正是如此!\\n&7[If you haven't played Minecraft since 1.13 this might confuse you, but you know Crossbows and Piercing. They have an enchantment which allows their Arrows to go through multiple targets and continuously dealing damage. This Module does exactly that!]&f"]
	quest.78FBB0C88182040E.title: "&a飞龙箭矢穿透模块&f&7[Wyvern Projectile Penetration Module]&f"
	quest.79886D63280DBBF3.quest_desc: ["过滤还不够？!？!你想销毁物品？!？!你这个怪物!\\n&7[Filtering isn't enough?!?! You want the items destroyed?!?! You monster!]&f"]
	quest.79886D63280DBBF3.title: "&a选择性焚烧模块&f&7[Selective Incineration Module]&f"
	quest.79FC674836B6340E.title: "&a神龙跳跃模块&f&7[Draconic Jump Module]&f"
	quest.7A4ABFCD12202A91.quest_desc: ["操作潜能是&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f的能量来源.移动OP的主要方式(不是唯一方式)是使用输入/输出中继水晶.要将OP实际输入物品,你需要一个&a能量传输&f.\\n&7[Operational Potential is the Energy source of Draconic Evolution. The main way (not the only way) of moving OP is with IO Relay Crystals. To actually get OP into items you'll need an Energy Transfer.]&f"]
	quest.7A4ABFCD12202A91.title: "什么是能量,或者我们称之为OP？&7[What is Energy or as we call it, OP?]&f"
	quest.7B9F5EEC76FDD0D4.title: "&a神龙伤害模块&f&7[Draconic Damage Module]&f"
	quest.7C54581562D2EA75.quest_desc: ["&a速度模块&f很有趣,它们几乎适用于所有物品,并使其更快!剑挥动更快,镐挖掘更快,斧砍伐更快,弓射击更快,胸甲让你移动更快.&a速度模块&f越好,速度就越快!(顺便提一下,现在是说明大多数属性可以叠加的好时机.2个基础&a速度模块&f可以将速度提高20%%!)\\n&7[Speed Modules are fun, they work in just about everything and make them faster! Swords swing faster, Pickaxes mine faster, Axes chop faster, Bows shoot faster, and Chestplate makes you faster. The better the Speed Module the faster they go! (BTW good time to mention most stats stack up. 2 Basic Speed Modules increase Speed by 20%% then!)]&f"]
	quest.7C54581562D2EA75.title: "基础&a速度模块&f&7[Basic Speed Module]&f"
	quest.7D159D333B2AC57E.quest_desc: [
		"5亿OP？检查完毕.燃料？检查完毕.热量达到2000°C？检查完毕.只需点击那个激活按钮,祈祷它不会熔毁!\\n&7[500 Million OP? Check. Fuel? Check. Heat at 2000 C? Check. Just click that activate button and pray it doesn't Meltdown!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_reactor_on_down.png width:200 height:100 align:1}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/draconic/draconic_reactor_on_up.png width:150 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.7D159D333B2AC57E.quest_subtitle: "现在我们祈祷并希望……&7[Now we pray and hope...]&f"
	quest.7D159D333B2AC57E.title: "激活反应堆&7[Activating the Reactor]&f"
	quest.7D7E4C31DFE59E29.quest_desc: ["这些模块仅适用于龙之研究的弓,与之前的模块不同.&a弹射物伤害&f模块增加弓射出的箭矢的伤害.有些模块会带来负面效果,比如这些模块会略微降低弓的精准度.所有这些都可以叠加!\\n&7[These Modules are only for the DE Bows, unlike the previous ones. The Projectile Damage Module increases the damage of Arrows shot by the Bow. Some Modules happen to have negative effects with it, like these give a slight more Inaccuracy to Bows. All of these can stack!]&f"]
	quest.7D7E4C31DFE59E29.title: "&a飞龙射击伤害模块&f&7[Wyvern Projectile Damage Module]&f"
	quest.7EB1C1AE52A0027F.title: "&a混沌箭矢重力修正模块&f&7[Chaotic Projectile Gravity Compensation Module]&f"
	quest.7EB97C0DDE60DED4.quest_desc: ["来自&d龙之进化/龙之研究&f的最佳弓,还拥有更多的模块槽位!\\n&7[Best Bow from Draconic Evolution, also with more Module slots!]&f"]
	quest.7EB97C0DDE60DED4.title: "&a混沌弓&f&7[Chaotic Bow]&f"
	quest.7F757CD6F8C57733.quest_desc: ["&a能量核心&f是Minecraft中,即使不是最伟大的,也是最伟大的能量存储库之一.一切都始于核心.这是&a能量核心&f多方块结构的中心和心脏(确保它稍微离地).当你放置它时,你可以看到它的GUI,包含:建造指南、降级、升级和&a组装核心&f.等级决定了核心的大小和功率.建造指南向你展示如何组装这个等级的核心.如果你拥有所有必要的方块,你可以按下&a组装核心&f,它会自动完成建造!\\n&7[The Energy Core is one, if not the, greatest Energy bank in all of Minecraft. And it all starts with the Core. This is the middle and heart of the Energy Core Multiblock (make sure it's a bit off the ground). When you place it down you can see it's GUI with the: Build Guide, Tier Down, Tier Up, and Assemble Core. The Tiers determine how big and powerful the Core is. The Build Guide shows you how to assemble this Tier of Core. If you have all the blocks necessary you can press Assemble Core and it will automatically make it!]&f"]
	quest.7F757CD6F8C57733.quest_subtitle: "龙之研究&a能量存储&f&7[Draconic Power Storage]&f"
	quest.7F757CD6F8C57733.title: "&a能量核心&f多方块结构&7[Energy Core Mulitblock]&f"
	task.1EFD3D7C04F9682A.title: "任务由AllTheMods提供&7[Quests By AllTheMods]&f"
	task.2AE8A0F6A6C2D453.title: "任务由AllTheMods提供&7[Quests By AllTheMods]&f"
	task.61CCAD2018478894.title: "激活&7[Activation]&f"
	task.664130FB28E419EF.title: "输入/输出水晶&7[I/O Crystals]&f"
	task.6EAC5BBFAA0184BC.title: "准备&7[Preparation]&f"
	quest.04A7AA70C23830FF.quest_desc: ["镰刀工具,可用于清除大量有机材料.镰刀会破坏你挖掘方块周围区域内的方块.\\n&7[Sickles tools that can be used to clear large amount of organic materials. Sickles break blocks in an area around the block you mine.]&f"]
	quest.04B6E31120663EB2.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.06EAA74E0A10CBB6.quest_subtitle: "范围:&b36&r格&7[Range: 36 Blocks]&f"
	quest.06EAA74E0A10CBB6.title: "&9英普瑞姆&a生长加速器&f&7[Imperium Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.07564DBB023EE2A6.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.077B2D62FA7650FB.quest_subtitle: "范围:&627&r格&7[Range: 27 Blocks]&f"
	quest.077B2D62FA7650FB.title: "&c特提姆&a生长加速器&f&7[Tertium Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.0B37355262121DD5.quest_desc: ["&a&a注魔祭坛&f&r是你制作所有种子的方式.首先放置祭坛,它会显示在哪里放置基座.\\n\\n为了使注魔开始,祭坛需要一个&4红石信号&r.\\n&7[The Infusion Altar is how you make all of the seeds. Place down the Altar first and it'll show you where to place the Pedestals after.\\n\\nIn order for the Infusing to start, the Alter requires a Redstone signal.]&f"]
	quest.0B37355262121DD5.quest_subtitle: "创造种子&7[Creating Seeds]&f"
	quest.0B37355262121DD5.title: "&4&a注魔祭坛吧&f&7[Infusion Altar]&f"
	quest.0EFEDB0DD90DFC81.quest_desc: ["&a收割机&f可以自动收割作物并重新种植.收割机收集的物品会放入其内部物品栏.\\n&7[The Harvester can auto-harvest crops and re-plant them. Items collected by the Harvester are put into it's internal inventory.]&f"]
	quest.13124A7E22999850.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.15D764CAF047EA7A.title: "&c特提姆盔甲&r&7[Tertium Armor]&f"
	quest.1609BF52108238B0.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.1636F3F12E92CAEA.quest_desc: [
		"要使用&a洒水壶&f,你需要通过右击水源方块来为其装满水.一旦装满水,你可以按住右击作物来浇灌&a洒水壶&f作用范围内的作物.\\n&7[To use a Watering Can you'll need to fill it with Water by right-clicking on a Water source block. Once it's filled with Water you can hold right-click on a crop to water the crops within the Watering Can's AOE.]&f"
		""
		"精华洒水壶具有自动浇水的功能.只需按住Shift键右击空中的&a洒水壶&f来&a切换设置&f自动浇水的开启或关闭.当开启时,&a洒水壶&f看起来像是&a已被附魔&f.\\n&7[Essence Watering cans have the ability of auto-watering. Just shift-right-click the Watering Can in the air to toggle auto-watering on or off. It will look like the Watering Can is enchanted when it's turned on.]&f"
	]
	quest.16E3031D800B40D5.quest_desc: ["&a灵魂&f刷怪笼使用生物精华来生成生物.例如,如果你放入一些&a恶魂精华&f,你可以生成一只恶魂.\\n&7[The Soulium Spawner uses mob essences to spawn mobs. For example if you put in some Ghast Essence you can spawn a Ghast.]&f"]
	quest.1C2CF6253F8B32EE.quest_subtitle: "等级:&56&7[Tier: 6]&f"
	quest.1C4ABF4518638A82.quest_desc: ["增益效果:\\n\\n - &a伤害吸收 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a速度 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a抗性提升 II&f (3:00)\\n - 生命恢复 II (3:00)\\n - &a力量 II&f (3:00)\\n&7[Buffs:\\n\\n - Absorption II (3:00)\\n - Speed II (3:00)\\n - Resistance II (3:00)\\n - Regeneration II (3:00)\\n - Strength II (3:00)]&f"]
	quest.1C4ABF4518638A82.title: "&4&a终极精华苹果&f&7[Supremium Apple]&f"
	quest.1CC4F8570A7A99EB.quest_desc: ["&d精华&r是你在&d神秘农业&f中所有种植需求的起点.\\n\\n&e下级精华&r是所有精华的基础等级.你可以通过挖掘、击杀生物或制作种子来种植它们来获得!\\n\\n要制作更大更好的精华,你需要制作一个&9&a注魔水晶&f&r.\\n&7[Essence is the starting point for all of your growing needs in Mystical Agriculture.\\n\\nInferium Essence is the base tier of all essences. You can get this from mining, killing mobs, or by making seeds to grow them! \\n\\nTo make the bigger and better essences, you'll need to make an Infusion Crystal. ]&f"]
	quest.1CC4F8570A7A99EB.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.1CC4F8570A7A99EB.title: "&a下级&7[Inferium]&f"
	quest.1CF8263756EE8F2A.quest_desc: ["这种特殊的&e粉尘&r由凋灵和&a末影龙&f在被附有&d神秘启迪&r的&d精华武器&r击杀时掉落.\\n&7[This special Dust is dropped from the Wither and the Ender Dragon when killed by an Essence Weapon enchanted with Mystical Enlightenment.]&f"]
	quest.1CF8263756EE8F2A.title: "&5认知粉尘&r&7[Cognizant Dust]&f"
	quest.1E0F92F07FDD162E.quest_desc: ["你需要&b&a活化种子基底&f&r来创造资源作物.\\n&7[You will need Prosperity Seed Bases in order to create resource crops.]&f"]
	quest.1E0F92F07FDD162E.quest_subtitle: "我专注于(种子)基底&7[I'm all about that (Seed) Base]&f"
	quest.1E0F92F07FDD162E.title: "&b&a活化种子基底&f&7[Prosperity Seed Base]&f"
	quest.1E414D285E7A5FE2.title: "&c特提姆工具&7[Tertium Tools]&f"
	quest.1E7DC8E0493BE99E.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.1F7591DB6D8EC1E7.quest_desc: ["增益效果:\\n\\n - &a伤害吸收 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a速度 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a抗性提升 II&f (3:00)\\n - 生命恢复 II (3:00)\\n - &a力量 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a急迫 II&f (3:00)\\n&7[Buffs:\\n\\n - Absorption II (3:00)\\n - Speed II (3:00)\\n - Resistance II (3:00)\\n - Regeneration II (3:00)\\n - Strength II (3:00)\\n - Haste II (3:00)]&f"]
	quest.1F7591DB6D8EC1E7.title: "&a&5究极苹果&f&7[Insanium Apple]&f"
	quest.1F88C697817A7680.quest_desc: ["增益效果:\\n\\n - &a伤害吸收 II&f (3:00)\\n&7[Buffs:\\n\\n - Absorption II (3:00)]&f"]
	quest.1F88C697817A7680.title: "&a下级苹果&7[Inferium Apple]&f"
	quest.202B1F54D3F06DAB.quest_desc: ["这是第6级精华,由4个至尊精华与一个&a注魔水晶&f结合制成.\\n&7[This is the Tier 6 Essence, made by combining 4 Supremium together with an Infusion Crystal.]&f"]
	quest.202B1F54D3F06DAB.quest_subtitle: "等级:&56&7[Tier: 6]&f"
	quest.202B1F54D3F06DAB.title: "&5无尽&7[Insanium]&f"
	quest.20851E0CF315F722.quest_desc: ["对于这个等级的种子,你需要在耕地下方放置一个相同类型的核心,种子才能生长.\\n&7[For seeds of this tier, you will need a crux of the same type placed below the farmland in order for the seeds to grow.]&f"]
	quest.20851E0CF315F722.title: "&5&a究极耕地&f&7[Insanium Farmland]&f"
	quest.212EF8601746C500.quest_desc: ["增益效果:\\n\\n - &a伤害吸收 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a速度 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a抗性提升 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a生命恢复 II&f (3:00)\\n&7[Buffs:\\n\\n - Absorption II (3:00)\\n - Speed II (3:00)\\n - Resistance II (3:00)\\n - Regeneration II (3:00)]&f"]
	quest.212EF8601746C500.title: "&9英普瑞姆苹果&7[Imperium Apple]&f"
	quest.21A90474590FCDB8.quest_desc: ["”熔炉”是原版熔炉的升级版本,可以进行升级以获得更快的速度和更高的效率.\\n&7[The \"Furnace\" is an upgraded version of a vanilla Furnace that can be upgraded for faster speed and better efficiency.]&f"]
	quest.21A90474590FCDB8.title: "”熔炉”&7[\"Furnace\"]&f"
	quest.224CE21E56703F6E.quest_desc: ["法杖可用于激活注魔祭坛,只需右键点击祭坛即可启动注魔过程.\\n&7[The Wand can be used to activate the Infusion Alter, just right-click on the altar to activate the infusion process.]&f"]
	quest.224CE21E56703F6E.quest_subtitle: "你是个巫师(填入你的名字)!&7[You're a Wizard (Insert your name)!]&f"
	quest.224CE21E56703F6E.title: "&2法杖&7[Wand]&f"
	quest.23C36E4B5DCEBFDD.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods 团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r创作,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均采用&e保留所有权利&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods 团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非其发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到了这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.260F9C98DC2E485B.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.26A7746051A4A079.quest_subtitle: "等级:&63&7[Tier: 3]&f"
	quest.27A0BCE75F198A82.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.27E8ED4B5F8127F9.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.29AE69722AB4C75C.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.2A59C2FE4AAA79D4.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.2A7E3F2CD335EAD0.quest_desc: ["要开始制作&a精华装备&r的旅程,你需要先制作下级精华盔甲.\\n\\n这套装备可以像精华一样升级到更高等级.你还可以用&b&a工具装配台&f&r为它们添加&9强化&r!\\n&7[To start your journey making Essence Gear, you'll need to make the Inferium Armor first.\\n\\nThis gear can be upgraded to higher tiers, just like the Essences. You can also Augment them with the Tinkering Table!]&f"]
	quest.2A7E3F2CD335EAD0.title: "&a下级精华盔甲&7[Inferium Armor]&f"
	quest.2AECDD9E2DEA708C.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.2C73E3C5113BF2AC.quest_desc: ["&a哔哔&f 我是一只羊\\n&7[Beep beep I'm a Sheep]&f"]
	quest.2C73E3C5113BF2AC.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.2C9C9CB71941DC01.quest_desc: ["这是第 3 级精华,由 4 个谨慎精华与一个&a注魔水晶&f合成而成.\\n&7[This is the Tier 3 Essence, made by combining 4 Prudentium together with an Infusion Crystal.]&f"]
	quest.2C9C9CB71941DC01.quest_subtitle: "等级:&63&7[Tier: 3]&f"
	quest.2C9C9CB71941DC01.title: "&c三级精华&7[Tertium]&f"
	quest.2DDA04088C8220D2.quest_desc: ["&a活化水晶碎片&f是模组中的核心合成材料.你可以通过用铁筛或更高级的筛子筛&a灵魂沙&f来获得它们.\\n&7[Prosperity Shards are a core crafting ingredient in the mod. You can obtain them by sifting Soul Sand with an Iron Sieve or higher.]&f"]
	quest.2DDA04088C8220D2.quest_subtitle: "我们终于能拥有繁荣了吗？&7[Can we finally have Prosperity?]&f"
	quest.2DDA04088C8220D2.title: "&b&a活化水晶碎片&f&7[Prosperity Shards]&f"
	quest.30E9255DEC69C061.title: "&4究极精华工具&7[Supremium Tools]&f"
	quest.32B01BD789F0B037.quest_desc: ["觉醒的究极精华和其他等级精华可以使用&6&d资源蜜蜂&f&r模组来自动化生产.\\n&7[Awakened Supremium and other tiered essences can be farmed using the Productive Bees mod.]&f"]
	quest.32B01BD789F0B037.title: "自动化觉醒的究极精华&7[Automating Awakened Supremium]&f"
	quest.3339445194568D77.title: "&2谨慎精华工具&7[Prudentium Tools]&f"
	quest.3384308C78D86059.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.33D23C65E7274A8F.quest_desc: ["要觉醒你的&a终极精华&f,你需要创建一个新的祭坛和 4 个新的基座,以及 4 个&c精华容器&r.\\n\\n&a精髓&f容器需要初始的元素精华来填充:火、水、土和风.\\n&7[To awaken your Supremium Essence, you'll need to create a new Altar and 4 new Pedestals, as well as 4 Essence Vessels.\\n\\nThe Essence Vessels will require the starter Element Essences to fill: Fire, Water, Earth, and Air.]&f"]
	quest.33D23C65E7274A8F.title: "&d觉醒&r&7[The Awakening]&f"
	quest.37B297640F537383.quest_desc: ["未调谐强化用于在注魔祭坛中创造各种强化.通过这些神奇的强化,你可以获得&e急迫&r、&1&a夜视&f&r、&b摔落&a伤害抵抗&f&r、&6&a火焰保护&f&r等等!\\n&7[The Unattuned Augment is used in an Infusion Alter to create various augments. Get Haste, Night Vision, Fall Damage Resistance, Fire Resistance, and much more with these amazing augments!]&f"]
	quest.37B297640F537383.title: "&f未调谐强化&7[Unattuned Augment]&f"
	quest.38A77DBAD24C4B53.quest_subtitle: "等级:&63&7[Tier: 3]&f"
	quest.398DEF6BA2E488C1.quest_subtitle: "等级:&56&7[Tier: 6]&f"
	quest.3BB3AA6C29285837.quest_desc: ["增益效果:\\n\\n - &a伤害吸收 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a速度 II&f (3:00)\\n&7[Buffs:\\n\\n - Absorption II (3:00)\\n - Speed II (3:00)]&f"]
	quest.3BB3AA6C29285837.title: "&2谨慎精华苹果&7[Prudentium Apple]&f"
	quest.3BD8315851A3EE5F.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.3C9F5EB59D72AC90.quest_desc: ["制作&6&aATM之星&f&r需要一个觉醒的&a终极精华锭&f块.\\n&7[An Awakened Supremium Ingot Block is needed to craft the ATM Star.]&f"]
	quest.3E555B364FD88B43.quest_subtitle: "范围:&c45&r 格&7[Range: 45 Blocks]&f"
	quest.3E555B364FD88B43.title: "&4&a终极生长加速器&f&7[Supremium Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.3EA2578C3A56FAE8.quest_desc: ["&a灵魂提取器&f允许你通过放入一个罐子并使用生物物品来填充&a灵魂瓶&f.例如,添加腐肉会给予一部分僵尸灵魂.\\n&7[The Soul Extractor allows you to fill up Soul Jars by inserting a jar and using mob items to fill them. For example, adding Rotten Flesh will give a portion of a Zombie Soul.]&f"]
	quest.3EBCBED3FD033117.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.408D8B1CFBA22BAF.quest_desc: ["防凋灵方块,&a防凋灵砖块&f和&a防凋零玻璃&f具有极高的爆炸抗性,不会被凋灵或&a末影龙&f摧毁.\\n&7[Witherproof Blocks, Witherproof Bricks and Witherproof Glass have a very high blast resistance and cannot be destroyed by the Wither or the Ender Dragon.]&f"]
	quest.408D8B1CFBA22BAF.title: "&0防凋灵方块&7[Witherproof Blocks]&f"
	quest.409A92D40F539485.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.41DBE44D7AA0B623.quest_desc: ["&a工具装配台&f就是用来为你的精华装备添加这些强化的!\\n&7[The Tinkering Table is how you add these augments to your essence gear!]&f"]
	quest.42218A7D42CF0A4C.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.4352505361D61BB2.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.4526E151BAE88310.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.4530C14828C3D153.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.45549E52B3CE2D23.quest_desc: ["镰刀是可以一次性收割大片作物的工具.它们也可以用作相当不错的武器.\\n&7[Scythes are tools that can farm large areas of crops all at once. They can also be used as a fairly good weapon.]&f"]
	quest.4821419D44F8083F.quest_desc: [
		"&9&a生长加速器&f&r当直接放置在耕地下方时,会略微增加种子的生长速度.每个等级都有其可以加速”向上”多少格的范围,下级精华的最低,为 12 格.\\n&7[Growth Accelerators very slightly increase the growth speed of a seed when placed directly underneath the farmland. Each tier has a range of how many blocks 'up' it can accelerate, with Inferium being the lowest at 12. ]&f"
		""
		"注意:所有等级的&a生长加速器&f提供相同的生长刻速率.然而,更高等级的范围更大,因此你可以在单个植物下方堆叠更多个.只要&a生长加速器&f放置在其最大范围内,使用哪个等级并不重要.\\n&7[Note: Growth Accelerators of all tiers provide the same rate of growth ticks. Higher tiers however have a larger range, so you can stack more of them below a single plant. It doesn't matter which tier you use as long as the Growth Accelerator is placed within its max range.]&f"
	]
	quest.4821419D44F8083F.quest_subtitle: "范围:&e9&r 格&7[Range: 9 Blocks]&f"
	quest.4821419D44F8083F.title: "&a下级精华 &a生长加速器&f&7[Inferium Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.48BF71269DEA1AB1.title: "&4&a终极耕地&f&7[Supremium Farmland]&f"
	quest.4EF5DE3FBA2A7AE3.quest_desc: ["从下级精华开始,你可以制作锭来制造精华&9工具&r和&9盔甲&r.\\n\\n精华工具可以升级到更高等级,就像盔甲一样,它们可以在&3&a工具装配台&f&r中进行&5强化&r.\\n&7[Starting with Inferium Essence, you can create ingots to make both Essence Tools and Armor.\\n\\nEssence tools can be upgraded to higher tiers, and just like the Armor, they can be Augmented in the Tinkering Table.]&f"]
	quest.4EF5DE3FBA2A7AE3.title: "&a下级精华工具&7[Inferium Tools]&f"
	quest.4F0DD86CF6E5F1B5.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.4F137DB561F45306.title: "&2谨慎精华盔甲&r&7[Prudentium Armor]&f"
	quest.52BB58D470560219.quest_subtitle: "范围:&c54&r 格&7[Range: 54 Blocks]&f"
	quest.52BB58D470560219.title: "&6Awakened &a终极生长加速器&f&7[Awakened Supremium Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.54735C5FCD2077B3.quest_desc: [
		"&a&d神秘农业&f&r是一个资源生成模组,允许你使用&a种子&r种植大量原版和模组资源.\\n&7[Mystical Agriculture is a resource generation mod that allows you to grow a large variety of vanilla and modded resources using Seeds.]&f"
		""
		"请注意,这个整合包中删除了很多种子,是的,我知道!我们怎么能这样？好吧,Geores 提供了一些替代方案,或许可以填补这个空白 ;)_\\n&7[Please note, alot of the seeds have been deleted in this modpack, yes I know! How could we? Well there are a few alternatives with Geores that might just fill that void ;)_]&f"
	]
	quest.54735C5FCD2077B3.title: "&a&d神秘农业&f!&7[Mystical Agriculture!]&f"
	quest.54D72C234EA76054.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.56201F98819478AB.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.576ABF43FCF886B7.title: "&2谨慎精华耕地&7[Prudentium Farmland]&f"
	quest.5782E9F866453D1D.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.5B1E0E3E876339E7.title: "&4究极精华盔甲&7[Supremium Armor]&f"
	quest.5BC4250E4C9F803C.title: "&9英普瑞姆耕地&7[Imperium Farmland]&f"
	quest.5C590DB2F3D935E5.quest_desc: ["&a种子再处理器&f可以将精华种子转化回精华.\\n&7[The Seed Reprocessor can convert essence seeds back into essences.]&f"]
	quest.5C590DB2F3D935E5.quest_subtitle: "回收利用!&7[Recycling!]&f"
	quest.5F6ACDE014A61F46.quest_desc: ["增益效果:\\n\\n - &a伤害吸收 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a速度 II&f (3:00)\\n - &a抗性提升 II&f (3:00)\\n&7[Buffs:\\n\\n - Absorption II (3:00)\\n - Speed II (3:00)\\n - Resistance II (3:00)]&f"]
	quest.5F6ACDE014A61F46.title: "&c三级精华苹果&7[Tertium Apple]&f"
	quest.617F1FA978197AFD.quest_subtitle: "等级:&56&7[Tier: 6]&f"
	quest.6235B9923BE0AAEB.quest_desc: ["&a附魔器&f是一个允许你使用物品和精华为可附魔物品添加附魔的方块.\\n&7[The Enchanter is a block that allows you to add enchantments to enchantable items using items and essences.]&f"]
	quest.6235B9923BE0AAEB.title: "&b附魔器&7[Enchanter]&f"
	quest.62D572BAB055F56F.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.6501A410F1543C70.quest_desc: ["&a魔法肥料&f的作用类似于骨粉,但效果更好.它能瞬间使使用对象生长至完全成熟.\\n&7[Mystical Fertilizer works as Bonemeal, but better. It instantly grows whatever it is used on to full maturity.]&f"]
	quest.6501A410F1543C70.title: "&a&d魔法肥料&f&7[Mystical Fertilizer]&f"
	quest.66C52B137A4FF869.quest_desc: ["这是第 4 级精华,由 4 个三级精华与一个&a注魔水晶&f合成而成.\\n&7[This is the Tier 4 Essence, made by combining 4 Tertium together with an Infusion Crystal.]&f"]
	quest.66C52B137A4FF869.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b4&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.66C52B137A4FF869.title: "&9英普瑞姆&7[Imperium]&f"
	quest.67DBE6C59C0D9D1B.quest_desc: ["这是第 4 级精华,由 4 个英普瑞姆与一个&a注魔水晶&f合成而成.\\n&7[This is the Tier 4 Essence, made by combining 4 Imperium together with an Infusion Crystal.]&f"]
	quest.67DBE6C59C0D9D1B.quest_subtitle: "等级:&c5&7[Tier: 5]&f"
	quest.67DBE6C59C0D9D1B.title: "&4究极精华&7[Supremium]&f"
	quest.67DDFA6FB1F9EECA.title: "&9英普瑞姆工具&7[Imperium Tools]&f"
	quest.685C4A646E092A82.title: "&6觉醒的究极精华盔甲&7[Awakened Supremium Armor]&f"
	quest.6A18B971C3DB83AE.quest_subtitle: "等级:&63&7[Tier: 3]&f"
	quest.712EB19B26D405DD.quest_subtitle: "等级:&e1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.73350AD668200E99.quest_desc: ["这是第 2 级精华,由 4 个下级精华与一个&a注魔水晶&f合成而成.\\n&7[This is the Tier 2 Essence, made by combining 4 Inferium together with an Infusion Crystal.]&f"]
	quest.73350AD668200E99.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.73350AD668200E99.title: "&2谨慎精华&7[Prudentium]&f"
	quest.75560045ED084900.quest_desc: [
		"大多数种子制作起来很简单,但要制作&9生物种子&r,你需要前往&a下界&f获取一些&8灵魂精华&r.\\n&7[Most seeds are simple to make, but to make Mob Seeds, you'll need to head to the Nether to pick up some Soulium. ]&f"
		""
		"用你找到的石头和矿石,你需要用它们制作&3&a灵魂匕首&f&r和&3&a灵魂瓶&f&r.使用匕首杀死生物,你将能够收集它们的&b灵魂&r,这些灵魂用于&a注魔祭坛吧&f来创建相应的生物种子.\\n&7[With the stone and ore that you find, you'll need to use these to make the Soulium Dagger and Soul Jars. Using the dagger to kill mobs, you'll be able to gather their souls, which are used in the Infusion Altar to create the respective mob seeds. ]&f"
		""
		"或者,你可以通过将罐子放入&3&a灵魂提取器&f&r并使用生物物品来填充&a灵魂瓶&f.例如,添加腐肉会给予一部分僵尸灵魂.\\n&7[Alternatively, you can fill Soul Jars inside of the Soul Extractor by inserting a jar and using mob items to fill them. For example, adding Rotten Flesh will give a portion of a Zombie Soul.]&f"
	]
	quest.75560045ED084900.title: "创建生物种子&7[Creating Mob Seeds]&f"
	quest.7580037DB8ADEB3C.quest_desc: ["喵喵,我是一头牛...\\n&7[Meow meow I'm a Cow...]&f"]
	quest.7580037DB8ADEB3C.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.76071C22A73A2026.title: "&c三级精华耕地&7[Tertium Farmland]&f"
	quest.7655E1C6C5E5469F.quest_subtitle: "范围:&a18&r 格&7[Range: 18 Blocks]&f"
	quest.7655E1C6C5E5469F.title: "&2谨慎精华 &a生长加速器&f&7[Prudentium Growth Accelerator]&f"
	quest.77C6667B4C37589C.quest_desc: ["机器升级用于加速&a&d神秘农业&f&r机器.\\n&7[Machine Upgrades are used to speed Mystical Agriculture machines.]&f"]
	quest.7A103577EAE7B3F1.quest_desc: ["这是第 5 级 - 觉醒精华,由 4 个认知粉尘、每种元素精华各 10 个和 1 个&a终极精华块&f在觉醒祭坛中合成而成.\\n&7[This is the Tier 5 - Awakened Essence, made by combining 4 Cognizant Dust, 10 of each Elemental Essence and 1 Supremium Block together in an Awakening Alter.]&f"]
	quest.7A103577EAE7B3F1.quest_subtitle: "等级:&c5 - 觉醒&7[Tier: 5 - Awakened]&f"
	quest.7A103577EAE7B3F1.title: "&6觉醒的究极精华&7[Awakened Supremium]&f"
	quest.7ADE214373DE135F.quest_subtitle: "等级:&63&7[Tier: 3]&f"
	quest.7BBD85F94D98CA46.quest_desc: ["大多数资源种子已被&c移除&r,以便为&b&a通量筛子&f&r (ExDeorum) 和带有&6&a生长加速器&f 等级&r的&aGeOres&r模组让路.\\n&7[Most Resource Seeds were removed to give way for Flux Sieves (ExDeorum) and GeOres mod with Growth Accelerator Tiers.]&f"]
	quest.7BBD85F94D98CA46.title: "警告&7[Warning]&f"
	quest.7CFA92CC48D1E7E3.quest_subtitle: "等级:&c5&7[Tier: 5]&f"
	quest.7D43016926E77150.title: "&9英普瑞姆盔甲&r&7[Imperium Armor]&f"
	quest.7DFF18CFEB0B8DBE.quest_desc: ["你应该尽快开始种植&a下级精华&r!\\n\\n虽然种植这些种子不一定需要,但你也可以创建&e&a精华耕地&f&r来增加种子的生长速度(尤其是&a究极精华种子&f).然而,某些种子需要种植在特定的耕地上.\\n&7[You'll want to start growing Inferium as soon as you can!\\n\\nWhile not required for growing these seeds, you can also create Essence Farmland that will increase the growth speed of the seeds (especially Inferium Seeds). However, certain seeds will require certain farmlands to be planted on.]&f"]
	quest.7DFF18CFEB0B8DBE.title: "&a下级精华耕地&7[Inferium Farmland]&f"
	task.011F410922A4D859.title: "镰刀&7[Scythes]&f"
	task.0C92F7E44100B2BA.title: "三级精华工具&7[Tertium Tools]&f"
	task.2DA0BD7B2834A560.title: "防凋灵方块&7[Witherproof Blocks]&f"
	task.323D34AF775A642B.title: "镰刀&7[Sickles]&f"
	task.34551E919FD101CF.title: "英普瑞姆工具&7[Imperium Tools]&f"
	task.3E133AC7B615971D.title: "究极精华工具&7[Supremium Tools]&f"
	task.41910A3BC6C0E838.title: "谨慎精华工具&7[Prudentium Tools]&f"
	task.4C906A47EBC15BC1.title: "&a洒水壶&f&7[Watering Cans]&f"
	task.4F6E8F2EC33DB910.title: "觉醒的究极精华工具&7[Awakened Supremium Tools]&f"
	task.518B9569DCE0A771.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.51A3E013D2B3D744.title: "机器升级&7[Machine Upgrades]&f"
	task.64FADC78A8AD3FE4.title: "种子&7[Seeds]&f"
	task.773CA1FDC4CEFCEF.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.7D9A58EBADE91F54.title: "下级精华工具&7[Inferium Tools]&f"
	quest.03164C4C7813CE2B.quest_desc: [
		"&a量子计算机&f是一个强大的合成CPU.只要它有可用的存储空间,它就能够运行无限的合成任务,并在它们之间共享协处理线程.\\n&7[The Quantum Computer is a powerful Crafting CPU. It is capable of running unlimited crafting jobs, and sharing co-processing threads among them, so long as it has storage available for it to use.]&f"
		""
		"它必须是一个至少3x3x3大小、最大7x7x7的长方体.或者:一个&a量子计算机&f核心本身就能成为一台&a量子计算机&f.\\n&7[It must be a cuboid of at least 3x3x3 size and up to 7x7x7. Alternatively: One Quantum Computer Core is capable of being a Quantum Computer by itself.]&f"
		""
		"一个&a量子计算机&f多方块结构需要满足以下条件:\\n&7[A Quantum Computer Multiblock requires the following:]&f"
		"- 多方块结构中不能有空隙.可以用量子合成单元填充,但没有额外好处.\\n&7[- No empty spaces can be present in the multiblock. They can be filled with Quantum Crafting Unit for no additional benefits.]&f"
		"- 恰好一个&a量子计算机&f核心\\n&7[- Exactly one Quantum Computer Core]&f"
		"- 最多一个量子数据纠缠器\\n&7[- At most one Quantum Data Entangler]&f"
		"- 最多一个&a量子计算机&f多线程器\\n&7[- At most one Quantum Computer Multi-Threader]&f"
		"- 最外层的所有方块必须是 &a量子计算机结构玻璃&f.\\n&7[- All blocks on the outside layer must be Quantum Computer Structural Glass]&f"
		"- 内部不能有任何 &a量子计算机结构玻璃&f 方块.\\n&7[- No blocks on the inside can be Quantum Computer Structural Glass.]&f"
		""
		"希望你准备好制造大量的奇点.\\n&7[Hope you're ready to make a lot of Singularities.]&f"
	]
	quest.03164C4C7813CE2B.title: "无限合成任务:&a量子计算机&f&7[Infinite Crafting Jobs: The Quantum Computer]&f"
	quest.034AB493E1EC2E63.quest_desc: [
		"&a装配机&f 矩阵核心决定了多方块结构的模式容量、合成任务和速度.\\n&7[The Assembler Matrix Cores are what determine the pattern capacity, crafting jobs, and speed of the multiblock.]&f"
		""
		"合成核心为多方块结构增加 8 个最大并行合成任务.\\n&7[Craft Cores add 8 maximum parallel crafting jobs to the multiblock.]&f"
		"模式核心为多方块结构增加 36 个模式槽位.\\n&7[Pattern Cores add 36 pattern slots to the multiblock.]&f"
		"速度核心的作用类似于 &a加速卡&f,可以提高合成任务的速度.安装超过 5 个速度核心不会对每个合成任务的速度产生额外影响.\\n&7[Speed Cores work like an Acceleration Card, increasing the speed of crafting jobs. Installing more than 5 Speed Cores does not have an effect on the speed of each crafting job.]&f"
	]
	quest.034AB493E1EC2E63.title: "装配机矩阵核心&7[Assembler Matrix Cores]&f"
	quest.07E5B0BF7D8E055A.quest_subtitle: "+30% 闪避几率&7[+30% Evasion Chance]&f"
	quest.09F43EB79DDBD127.quest_desc: [
		"&a量子&f 数据纠缠器允许物品存储在多个维度,有效地将 &a量子计算机&f 多方块结构中的合成存储乘以 4.例如,一个 256M 的量子合成存储现在将提供 1G 的合成存储.\\n&7[The Quantum Data Entangler allows items to be stored in multiple dimensions, effectively multiplying crafting storage in a Quantum Computer Multiblock by 4. For example, a 256M quantum crafting storage will now give 1G Crafting Storage.]&f"
		""
		"&l在一个 &a量子计算机&f 多方块结构中,你只能拥有 1 个此方块.\\n&7[lYou can only have 1 of these in a Quantum Computer Multiblock.]&f"
	]
	quest.09F43EB79DDBD127.title: "不必要的大存储:量子数据纠缠器&7[Unnecessarily Large Storage: Quantum Data Entangler]&f"
	quest.0A354B4707894A62.quest_subtitle: "最高 +3 &a跳跃高度&f&7[Up to +3 Jump Height]&f"
	quest.0B4CE3969067FA31.quest_desc: [
		"&a量子&f 盔甲可以通过各种不同的升级进行强化.\\n&7[The Quantum Armor can be upgraded with a variety of different upgrades.]&f"
		""
		"要升级你的量子盔甲,请按下其对应的按键(默认为 N)打开量子盔甲配置菜单.\\n&7[To upgrade your Quantum Armor, open the Quantum Armor Configuration Menu by pressing its respective keybind (N by default).]&f"
	]
	quest.0B4CE3969067FA31.title: "量子盔甲升级&7[Upgrades for Quantum Armor]&f"
	quest.0D8B4DAB82ABEF9D.quest_desc: ["量子加速器为 &a量子计算机&f 多方块结构各增加 8 个协处理线程.需要注意的是,&a量子计算机&f 运行的所有合成任务都能够共享所有协处理器,因此大量投资这些加速器是个好主意.\\n&7[Quantum Accelerators add 8 co-processing threads each to the Quantum Computer multiblock. It's important to note that all crafting jobs being run by the Quantum Computer are able to share all co-processors, so it's a good idea to invest in a great amount of these.]&f"]
	quest.0D8B4DAB82ABEF9D.title: "协&a处理&f 遗忘:&a量子计算机&f 加速器&7[Co-Processing Oblivion: Quantum Computer Accelerator]&f"
	quest.0E06F323BF8C1D73.quest_desc: [
		"考虑到萌芽熵化福鲁伊克斯的衰变不可避免,你可能需要一些其他方法来自动种植它们.\\n&7[Given the inevitability of the decay of Budding Entroized Fluix, you might want some other ways to automatically farm them.]&f"
		""
		"幸运的是,有一种蜜蜂可以做到.\\n&7[Fortunately, there's a bee for that.]&f"
	]
	quest.0E06F323BF8C1D73.quest_subtitle: "当你无法处理衰变时&7[For when you can't deal with decay]&f"
	quest.0E06F323BF8C1D73.title: "自动化熵水晶&7[Automating Entro Crystals]&f"
	quest.12749A25600C7FF3.quest_desc: [
		"&a量子&f 合成器是一个强大且可配置的自动合成器.它掌握着整个 ME 网络的物品栏,不间断地合成变成了一项微不足道的任务.它能够以非常快的速度运行合成任务.它还能够进行流体替换以及递归合成(例如 &a锻造模板&f 复制).\\n&7[The Quantum Crafter is a powerful and configurable auto-crafter. With an entire inventory of an ME network at its grasp, crafting non-stop becomes a trivial task. It is capable of running crafting jobs at a very fast pace. It is also capable of running fluid substitutions as well as recursive crafts (such as Smithing Template Duplication).]&f"
		""
		"你还可以调节你想要保留的每种原料的数量,以及你想要保留多少成品库存.\\n&7[You can also regulate how much of each ingredient you want to keep, and up to how many of the product you want to keep in stock.]&f"
		""
		"不过,它不会接受来自模式供应器的合成请求.\\n&7[Won't accept crafting requests from Pattern Providers, though.]&f"
	]
	quest.12749A25600C7FF3.title: "全自动合成:&a量子&f 合成器&7[Fully Automated Crafting: The Quantum Crafter]&f"
	quest.14FC9E4A3C80C0AE.quest_desc: [
		"&a反应仓&f 能够在其内部加速各种世界内反应,使用催化剂流体和大量能量.由于受控的环境,这台机器能够使所述反应更加高效,让你从中获得更多材料.\\n&7[The Reaction Chamber is capable of accelerating various In-World Reactions within itself, using a catalyst fluid and great amounts of power. Due to the controlled environment, this machine is capable of making said reactions more efficient, allowing you to gain more material out of them.]&f"
		""
		"不过,这台机器相当耗电,强烈建议在你的 ME 网络中配备良好的发电设备和能量单元.\\n&7[This machine is quite power hungry, though, good power generation and energy cells in your ME Network are highly recommended.]&f"
		""
		"这台机器也是高级 AE 中量子相关配方所必需的.\\n&7[This machine is also required for Quantum related recipes in Advanced AE.]&f"
	]
	quest.14FC9E4A3C80C0AE.title: "反应效率:&a反应仓&f&7[Reaction Efficiency: The Reaction Chamber]&f"
	quest.18499D33BA12A8A9.quest_desc: ["是否曾觉得 &a成型面板&f 像存储总线一样工作对于自动化来说太不直观了？看看主动 &a成型面板&f 吧.它的工作原理类似于 ME 输出总线,但它将世界视为其媒介.你不需要为这个设备设置子网络.\\n&7[Ever thought that Formation Planes acting like a Storage Bus was way too unintuitive for automation? Look no further than the Active Formation Plane. It works like an ME Export Bus but it treats the world as its medium. You don't need a subnet for this one.]&f"]
	quest.18499D33BA12A8A9.quest_subtitle: "出去:主动版&7[GET OUT: Active Edition]&f"
	quest.18499D33BA12A8A9.title: "从 &a网络&f 主动放置:主动 &a成型面板&f&7[Actively Placing From The Network: The Active Formation Plane]&f"
	quest.1A20BBBAFBEDF911.quest_desc: [
		"&a量子计算机&f 多线程器将 &a量子计算机&f 多方块结构中的协处理线程乘以 4.例如:一个 &a量子计算机&f 加速器在多方块结构中有此方块时将提供 32 个协处理线程.\\n&7[The Quantum Computer Multi-Threader multiplies co-processing threads in the Quantum Computer Multiblock by 4. For example: A Quantum Computer Accelerator will give 32 co-processing threads with this block in the multiblock.]&f"
		""
		"&l在一个 &a量子计算机&f 多方块结构中,你只能拥有一个 &a量子计算机&f 多线程器.&r\\n&7[lYou can only have one Quantum Computer Multi-Threader in a Quantum Computer Multiblock.]&f"
	]
	quest.1A20BBBAFBEDF911.title: "协&a处理&f 至无限:&a量子计算机&f 多线程器&7[Co-Processing To Infinity: Quantum Computer Multi-Threader]&f"
	quest.1A815711703E4A24.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 工作人员&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 编写,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均在 &e保留所有权利&r 许可下授权,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不允许在任何非 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 发布的公开整合包中使用.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.1B90B94D07BBDD09.quest_desc: [
		"要制造所有这些 ExtendedAE 设备,工作台的锤子和钳子是不够的.\\n&7[To make all these ExtendedAE devices, a Crafting Table's hammer and pliers won't cut it.]&f"
		""
		"是时候升级到水晶组装机了,这是一台能够处理这些复杂操作的机器.\\n&7[It's time we upgrade to the Crystal Assembler, a machine capable of handling these complex operations.]&f"
		""
		"有了这些,你就可以组装 ExtendedAE 的各种设备.\\n&7[With these, you can assemble the various devices of ExtendedAE.]&f"
		""
		"这些机器也能够处理世界内反应,但不如 &a反应仓&f 好,并且还能够一次组装 4 个处理器.\\n&7[These are also capable of handling In-World Reactions, but not quite as well as the Reaction Chamber, and also capable of assembling processors, 4 at a time.]&f"
		""
		"有屏幕的一面不能连接到 ME 网络.\\n&7[The face that has a screen can't connect to an ME Network.]&f"
	]
	quest.1B90B94D07BBDD09.title: "复杂合成器:&a水晶&f 组装机&7[Complex Crafter: The Crystal Assembler]&f"
	quest.1E535784A9D3DE89.quest_desc: ["这些是 ExtendedAE 中不需要熵水晶的物品.\\n&7[These are things from ExtendedAE that don't require Entro Crystals.]&f"]
	quest.27FC0C092EE00532.quest_desc: ["ME 灌装机可以填充或清空能够容纳流体、化学品、能量的容器,例如桶、化学品储罐等.如果使用模式来填充它们,它会自动输出到模式供应器.\\n&7[The ME Canner can fill or empty containers that can contain fluids, chemicals, energy, such as buckets, chemical tanks, and more. It automatically outputs to pattern providers if a pattern is used to fill them.]&f"]
	quest.27FC0C092EE00532.quest_subtitle: "不要与 ME 罐头机混淆&7[not to be confused with the me caner]&f"
	quest.27FC0C092EE00532.title: "能装这种液体:ME 灌装机&7[Can this Liquid: The ME Canner]&f"
	quest.2E61219FC0BAB675.quest_subtitle: "最高 +5 触及距离&7[Up to +5 Reach]&f"
	quest.3347CB6478F486C6.quest_subtitle: "&a元件工作台&f 随你而行&7[Cell Workbench Wherever You Go]&f"
	quest.33B7C1D2A229EB5C.quest_desc: ["是否曾想要终极的 &a量子计算机&f 配置？好吧,这里有一个为你准备的配置,专注于最大化协处理线程.\\n\\n我们需要 218 个 &a量子计算机结构玻璃&f、123 个 &a量子计算机&f 加速器、1 个 &a量子计算机&f 核心和 1 个 &a量子计算机&f 多线程器.这总共给我们 8928 个协处理线程.请注意,除了核心之外,我没有在这里包含任何存储,因为核心自带的 256M 合成存储已经足够了.数据纠缠器任务是可选的是有原因的.\\n\\n获得 200 个量子计算机结构玻璃和 100 个量子计算机加速器,我会给你剩下的,因为我和 &d神化附魔&f 章节一样慷慨.\\n&7[Ever wanted the ultimate Quantum Computer setup? Well, here's a setup for you, focused on maximizing co-processing threads.\\n\\n218 Quantum Computer Structural Glass, 123 Quantum Computer Accelerators, 1 Quantum Computer Core, and 1 Quantum Computer Multi-Threader are what we need. This gives us a total of 8928 co-processing threads. Note that I did not include any storage here besides the core, as the 256M crafting storage from the core is plenty enough already. The Data Entangler quest is optional for a reason.\\n\\nGet 200 Q.C. Structural Glass and 100 Q.C. Accelerators, and I'll give you the rest, because I'm just as generous as the Apothic Enchanting chapter.]&f"]
	quest.33B7C1D2A229EB5C.title: "终极 &a量子计算机&f&7[The Ultimate Quantum Computer]&f"
	quest.34FBD04361657724.quest_desc: [
		"在整个 ExtendedAE 中,你将经常使用 &a熵水晶 &r作为资源.\\n&7[Throughout ExtendedAE, you will often be using Entro Crystals as a resource.]&f"
		""
		"要获得 &a熵水晶&r,你需要一个 &a福鲁伊克斯块&f 和一个熵种子.用熵种子 &a右击&f &a福鲁伊克斯块&f.\\n&7[To get the Entro Crystal, you will need a Fluix Block and an Entro Seed. Right Click the Fluix Block with the Entro Seed.]&f"
		""
		"这将创建 &a萌芽熵化福鲁伊克斯&r,它会像萌芽 &a赛特斯石英&f 一样,在其周围生长熵芽.与赛特斯石英不同,它的衰变是不可避免的.\\n&7[This will create Budding Entroized Fluix, which will, similarly to Budding Certus Quartz, grow Entro Buds around it. Unlike with Certus, its decay is inevitable.]&f"
		""
		"&a萌芽熵化福鲁伊克斯&r 在被破坏时总是会掉落 &l一个 &r&a熵粉&r,无论其处于何种状态.未完全生长的熵芽会掉落熵碎片.\\n&7[Budding Entroized Fluix will always drop lone Entro Dust when broken, regardless of the state it's in. Entro Buds will drop Entro Shards when they aren't fully grown.]&f"
	]
	quest.34FBD04361657724.quest_subtitle: "不要与时间水晶混淆&7[not to be confused with time crystals]&f"
	quest.34FBD04361657724.title: "空间与时间的 &a水晶&f:熵水晶&7[The Crystals of Space and Time: Entro Crystals]&f"
	quest.3621155A4138EBCA.quest_desc: [
		"虚空单元在使用前需要在 &a元件工作台&f 中进行分区(过滤).它会删除进入 ME 系统的任何匹配过滤器的物品(假设虚空单元被优先处理),或者将它们压缩成 &a物质球&f 或奇点,类似于 &a物质聚合器&f.\\n&7[The Void Cell needs to be partitioned (filtered) in a Cell Workbench before using. It will delete anything that enters the ME system that matches the filter (assuming the void cell is prioritized), or condenses them into Matter Balls or Singularities, similarly to the Matter Condenser.]&f"
		""
		"&a右击&f 它以打开配置 GUI.\\n&7[Right click it to open the configuration GUI.]&f"
	]
	quest.3621155A4138EBCA.title: "单元中的 &a物质聚合器&f:虚空单元&7[Matter Condenser in a Cell: The Void Cell]&f"
	quest.36FB694262102CFD.quest_desc: [
		"ExtendedAE 提供了一种新型单元:无限单元.\\n&7[ExtendedAE offers a new type of cell, the Infinity Cell.]&f"
		""
		"这些单元提供特定类型资源的无限供应,例如水、圆石、熔岩等.\\n&7[These cells provide a limitless supply of a certain type of resource, such as Water, Cobblestone, Lava, etc.]&f"
	]
	quest.36FB694262102CFD.quest_subtitle: "水槽,但是单元形式&7[The Sink but in cell form]&f"
	quest.36FB694262102CFD.title: "比你需要的更多资源:无限单元&7[More Resources than you ever need: Infinity Cells]&f"
	quest.38D0BBD5F699EF41.quest_desc: ["如果连接到无线访问点,允许量子盔甲部件从你的 ME 系统能量中充电.如果放入 &a量子胸甲&f,它还会为你物品栏中的物品充电.这与 AppliedFlux 有特殊的交互,如果你在网络中有 FE 单元,它将从中提取能量.\\n&7[Allows the Quantum Armor piece to charge from your ME system's energy if linked to a Wireless Access Point. If placed into a Quantum Chestplate, it also recharges items in your inventory. This has a special interaction with AppliedFlux, where, if you have FE Cells in the network, it will extract energy from those.]&f"]
	quest.3916B48D7F294932.quest_desc: ["ME 无线集线器是 ME 无线连接器的升级版.它现在可以连接到 8 个不同的无线连接器或集线器.请注意,集线器总共只能传输 32 个频道.\\n&7[The ME Wireless Hub is an upgrade to the ME Wireless Connector. It can now connect to 8 different Wireless Connectors or Hubs. Note that the Hub can only transfer 32 channels in total.]&f"]
	quest.3916B48D7F294932.title: "连接的分支:无线集线器&7[Branches of Connections: The Wireless Hub]&f"
	quest.3972EE0ECB215843.quest_desc: ["Extended 和 Advanced AE 是 &d应用能源2&f 的附属模组.两者都专注于改善你的体验,添加各种设备的改进版本,以及更多内容.\\n&7[Extended and Advanced AE are addons for Applied Energistics 2. Both of them focus on improving your experience, adding improved versions of various devices, and more.]&f"]
	quest.3972EE0ECB215843.title: "扩展 \\ 高级 AE&7[Extended \\\\ Advanced AE]&f"
	quest.3B3F1DE1AF6EBC1E.quest_subtitle: "+10 力量&7[+10 Strength]&f"
	quest.3CF32F2314839B1D.quest_desc: [
		"厌倦了你的萌芽 &a赛特斯石英&f 和熵化福鲁伊克斯衰变吗？我们可以修复它!使用这个水晶修复器,你可以用充能 &a赛特斯石英&f 修复萌芽赛特斯水晶,用 &a末影尘&f 修复熵化福鲁伊克斯.\\n&7[Getting tired of your budding Certus Quartz and Entroized Fluix decaying? We can fix it! With this Crystal Fixer, you can fix Budding Certus Crystals with Charged Certus Quartz, and Entroized Fluix with Ender Dust.]&f"
		""
		"它甚至有小概率制造出无瑕的萌芽 &a赛特斯石英&f.\\n&7[It even has a small chance to make Flawless Budding Certus Quartz.]&f"
	]
	quest.3CF32F2314839B1D.title: "修复你的水晶:&a水晶&f 修复器&7[Get-Yer-Crystals-Fixed: The Crystal Fixer]&f"
	quest.3FE739EA7E297DF3.quest_desc: [
		"扩展设备是 AE2 设备的变体,它们要么容量更高,速度更快,或者两者兼有.\\n&7[Extended Devices are variants of AE2 devices that either have a higher capacity, are faster, and maybe even both.]&f"
		""
		"例如:&a扩展&f 模式供应器有 36 个模式槽位,是普通模式供应器的 &a4 倍&f.\\n&7[For example: The Extended Pattern Provider has 36 pattern slots, 4 times as many as an ordinary Pattern Provider.]&f"
		""
		"或者扩展输出/输入总线,它们的工作速度比普通的大约快 8 倍,并且支持更多升级.\\n&7[Or the Extended Export/Import Buses, they work about 8x faster than a regular one, and support more upgrades.]&f"
		""
		"由于这些大多数只是基础版本的升级版,我不会为每一个单独制作任务.\\n&7[As most of these are just upgraded versions of the base version, I won't be making separate quests for each individual one.]&f"
	]
	quest.3FE739EA7E297DF3.title: "更快更大:扩展设备&7[Faster and Bigger: Extended Devices]&f"
	quest.411A463E98C3B102.quest_desc: [
		"制造 &a量子计算机&f、合成器和盔甲所需的一些原料.\\n&7[Some ingredients you'll need to make the Quantum Computer, Crafter, and Armor.]&f"
		""
		"破碎奇点由 1 个奇点、2 个 &a末影尘&f、2 个 &a陨石粉&f 和 100 mB 熔岩在 &a反应仓&f 中制成.\\n&7[Shattered Singularity is made with a Singularity, 2 Ender Dust, 2 Sky Stone Dust, and 100 mB of Lava in a Reaction Chamber.]&f"
		""
		"1 桶量子灌注液由 4 桶水和 1 个量子灌注粉制成,量子灌注粉通过在压印机或 &d通用机械&f 粉碎机中粉碎破碎奇点获得.\\n&7[1 bucket of Quantum Infusion is made with 4 buckets of Water and a Quantum Infused Dust, which is obtained by crushing the Shattered Singularity in an Inscriber or Mekanism Crusher.]&f"
		""
		"量子 &a灌注合金&f 由 1 桶量子灌注液、4 个 &a铜锭&f、4 个破碎奇点和 4 个普通奇点制成.\\n&7[Quantum Infused Alloy is made with 1 bucket of Quantum Infusion, 4 Copper Ingots, 4 Shattered and 4 regular Singularities.]&f"
	]
	quest.411A463E98C3B102.title: "量子原料&7[Quantum Ingredients]&f"
	quest.4818C8387C0DBBE7.quest_desc: [
		"ExtendedAE 是 &d应用能源2&f 的一个附属模组,专注于添加各种设备的改进版本,并带回一些旧版 AE2 的功能.\\n&7[ExtendedAE is an addon for Applied Energistics 2, focused on adding improved versions of various devices, and bringing back some features from older versions of AE2.]&f"
		""
		"要开始,先获得一个 &a福鲁伊克斯块&f.\\n&7[To get started, get a Fluix Block.]&f"
	]
	quest.4818C8387C0DBBE7.title: "扩展应用能源&7[ExtendedAE]&f"
	quest.48357A7486125C52.quest_desc: [
		"厌倦了压印机的缓慢速度？\\n&7[Tired of the slow speed of the Inscriber?]&f"
		""
		"我们隆重推出芯片切片机!它能将金块等方块切片成芯片,一次最多可制作9个芯片(对于赛特斯石英或熵金,则为4个).\\n&7[We present the Circuit Slicer! It can slice blocks such as Gold Blocks into circuits, making up to 9 circuits at a time (or 4 in the case of certus or entro).]&f"
		""
		"芯片切片机没有端口的那一面玻璃无法连接到ME网络.\\n&7[The glass faces of the Circuit Slicer that don't have a port can't connect to an ME Network.]&f"
	]
	quest.48357A7486125C52.title: "方块变芯片:&a芯片&f切片机&7[Blocks to Circuits: The Circuit Slicer]&f"
	quest.4AC3EA41234BC5F0.quest_subtitle: "+20 最大生命值&7[+20 Max HP]&f"
	quest.52CD31F48715B17C.quest_desc: [
		"ME无线连接器可用于无线连接ME网络的两个点,类似于量子桥.但与量子桥不同,它只能连接大约1000格范围内的无线连接器,并且无法跨维度连接.\\n&7[The ME Wireless Connector can be used to connect two points of an ME Network wirelessly, similarly to the Quantum Bridge. Unlike the Quantum Bridge, it can only connect to Wireless Connectors up to about 1000 blocks away, and cannot connect across dimensions.]&f"
		""
		"&l要建立连接,请使用无线设置套件对准你想要连接的两个无线连接器.&r\\n&7[lTo set up a connection, use a Wireless Setup Kit on the two Wireless Connectors you want to link.]&f"
		""
		"你也可以使用&a染色器&f更改无线连接器的颜色.这将使其不会连接到不同颜色的线缆或无线连接器.\\n&7[You can also change the color of a Wireless Connector with the Color Applicator. This will make it not connect to cables or Wireless Connectors of a different color.]&f"
	]
	quest.52CD31F48715B17C.title: "远距离连接:无线连接器&7[Connections across long distances: The Wireless Connector]&f"
	quest.534D827A628907F4.quest_desc: [
		"&a扩展&f样板&a访问终端&f与普通样板&a访问终端&f功能相同,但增加了3个额外功能.\\n&7[The Extended Pattern Access Terminal works the same as the regular Pattern Access Terminal, but with 3 additional features.]&f"
		""
		"&l&n改进的样板搜索&r\\n&7[lImproved Pattern Search]&f"
		""
		"你可以通过输入/输出材料的名称来搜索样板.\\n&7[You can search for a pattern by input/output ingredients' name.]&f"
		""
		"&l&n样板高亮&r\\n&7[lPattern Highlight]&f"
		""
		"有时,由于样板在界面中分组显示的方式,仍然很难找到你想要的样板.使用此终端,你正在寻找的样板将在GUI中高亮显示.\\n&7[Sometimes, due to how patterns are displayed in a group, it is still hard to find the pattern you are looking for. With this terminal, the pattern you are looking for will be highlighted in the GUI.]&f"
		""
		"&l&n样板供应器世界内高亮&r\\n&7[lPattern Provider In-World Highlight]&f"
		""
		"在进行大型合成任务时,找出哪个样板供应器卡住了可能很烦人.&a扩展&f样板&a访问终端&f可以在世界中高亮显示样板供应器,让你更容易定位它.\\n&7[It can be annoying to find out which of your Pattern Providers are stuck when doing large crafting jobs. The Extended Pattern Access Terminal can highlight the Pattern Providers in world, making it easier to locate it.]&f"
	]
	quest.534D827A628907F4.title: "更好的样板访问:&a扩展&f样板&a访问终端&f&7[Better Pattern Access: The Extended Pattern Access Terminal]&f"
	quest.55DFC96B4CDBFA7D.quest_desc: ["&a量子计算机&f核心是&a量子计算机&f的心脏.它本身拥有256M合成存储和8个协处理线程.当通过其上下两侧(即连接器所在面)供能时,它也是唯一能够单独构成一个&a量子计算机&f的方块.然而,如果用于创建多方块结构,则可以创建出更强大的计算机.\\n&7[The Quantum Computer Core is the heart of the Quantum Computer. It has 256M crafting storage and 8 co-processing threads by itself. It is also the only block capable of forming a Quantum Computer by itself, when powered through the Up or Down sides, where the connectors are. However, if used to create a multiblock, a much more powerful computer can be created.]&f"]
	quest.55DFC96B4CDBFA7D.title: "合成之心:&a量子计算机&f核心&7[Heart of the Crafts: Quantum Computer Core]&f"
	quest.56DE217FEAE3F036.quest_desc: [
		"ME高级样板供应器是一种新型的ME样板供应器,它升级了标准或扩展样板供应器,使其能够配置样板中每种材料被发送到的机器面.这使得自动化那些需要特定面输入特定材料的机器成为可能,只需一个方块,无需管道或子网络,例如来自&d通用机械&f的&a冶金灌注机&f.\\n&7[The ME Advanced Pattern Provider is a new type of ME Pattern Provider that upgrades a standard or Extended Pattern Provider with the ability to configure the face to which any individual item in a pattern is sent to. This allows for automation of machines that require specific sides for specific inputs to be done with a single block and no pipes or a subnet, such as with the Metallurgic Infuser from Mekanism.]&f"
		""
		"要利用此功能,你需要一个高级&a样板编码台&f,来决定将每种材料发送到机器的哪个面.\\n&7[To make use of this feature, you need an Advanced Pattern Encoder, to decide which side of the machine to send each ingredient.]&f"
	]
	quest.56DE217FEAE3F036.quest_subtitle: "&a朝向&f you, &d通用机械&f&7[Looking at you, Mekanism]&f"
	quest.56DE217FEAE3F036.title: "指定面输入样板:高级样板供应器&7[Specific Sided Patterns: The Advanced Pattern Provider]&f"
	quest.5E610C059737628B.quest_subtitle: "最高+3 &a上坡高度&f&7[Up to +3 Step Height]&f"
	quest.6033ABA2088BA70C.quest_subtitle: "无飞行漂移&7[No Flight Drift]&f"
	quest.6559C57A1A476489.quest_subtitle: "+5 &a攻击速度&f&7[+5 Attack Speed]&f"
	quest.658DEAAD1E68E549.quest_desc: ["这些方块扩展了&a量子核心&f的合成存储.它们有效地增加了&a量子计算机&f能够同时运行的任务数量.它们也是制造&a量子计算机&f核心所必需的.\\n&7[These blocks expand the crafting storage of the Quantum Core. They effectively increase the amount of concurrent tasks the Quantum Computer is able to run. They are also required to make a Quantum Computer Core.]&f"]
	quest.658DEAAD1E68E549.title: "海量合成存储:&a量子计算机&f存储&7[Massive Crafting Storage: The Quantum Computer Storage]&f"
	quest.67C7EF299BEC37DE.quest_subtitle: "创造模式飞行&7[Creative Flight]&f"
	quest.763A19067AEEF6D5.quest_subtitle: "+2 幸运&7[+2 Luck]&f"
	quest.7725CB7D0AE55180.quest_desc: [
		"高级AE是&d应用能源2&f的一个附属模组,专注于改善你处理ME系统时的用户体验,并扩展终局系统的可能性.\\n&7[Advanced AE is an addon for Applied Energistics 2, that focuses on improving user experience whenever you handle your ME System and expanding the possibilities of end game systems.]&f"
		""
		"从可以向机器特定面推送材料的样板供应器,到能够运行无限合成任务、在这些合成任务间共享协处理器的多方块计算机,以及介于两者之间的一切.\\n&7[From a Pattern Provider that can push to specific sides of a machine, to a multiblock computer that is capable of running unlimited crafting jobs, sharing co-processors among said crafts, and anything in between.]&f"
	]
	quest.7725CB7D0AE55180.title: "高级AE&7[Advanced AE]&f"
	quest.78215D704E6095B0.quest_desc: ["你以为&5&l&d通用机械&f&r和&l&7&d现代工业化&f&r的终局盔甲套装就能独占所有乐趣吗？\\n\\n这套&5量子盔甲&r的默认属性与&c下界合金盔甲&r相似,但就像&aMekaSuit&r一样,它可以使用能量作为护盾.\\n它还有可以安装的升级,让你变得更强大!比如飞行、&a夜视&f,甚至充电能力.\\n\\n但最棒的是,它可以&a链接到&f你的存储系统!这样,无论你在哪里,都可以自动从中提取能量,并取出任何物品.\\n\\n此外,穿戴全套可以防止&a辐射&r杀死你.\\n&7[You think lMekanism and lModern Industrialization can have all the fun with their end game armor sets? \\n\\nThis Quantum Armor has default stats similar to Netherite Armor but, like the MekaSuit it can use Energy as a shield. \\nIt also has upgrades which can be installed to make you even more powerful! Like Flight, Night Vision, and even the ability to recharge. \\n\\nBut the best part is that it can Linked to your Storage System! Then, you can automatically take Energy out from it and take out any Item from it no matter where you are. \\n\\nFurthermore, wearing the full set can prevent Radiation from killing you.]&f"]
	quest.78215D704E6095B0.quest_subtitle: "不会让你完全无敌&7[Won't make you fully invincible]&f"
	quest.78215D704E6095B0.title: "ME系统即盔甲:&a量子&f盔甲&7[ME System As Armor: The Quantum Armor]&f"
	quest.7900A4836CC55428.quest_desc: [
		"&a装配机&f矩阵是一个多方块结构,可以有效地容纳多个&a分子装配室&f和样板供应器,且只占用一个频道.\\n&7[The Assembler Matrix is a multiblock that can effectively contain multiple Molecular Assemblers and Pattern Providers, all in one channel.]&f"
		""
		"&a装配机&f矩阵必须至少是一个3x3x3的长方体,最大可以是7x7x7的长方体.它需要以下部件:\\n&7[The Assembler Matrix must be at least a 3x3x3 cuboid and up to a 7x7x7 cuboid. It requires the following parts:]&f"
		"- 由装配机&a矩阵框架&f构成的边\\n&7[- Edges composed of Assembler Matrix Frames]&f"
		"- 由装配机矩阵墙/玻璃构成的面\\n&7[- Faces composed of Assembler Matrix Wall/Glass]&f"
		"- 由装配机矩阵样板/合成/速度核心构成的内部\\n&7[- Interior composed of Assembler Matrix Pattern/Craft/Speed Core]&f"
		""
		"一个有效的装配机矩阵必须至少包含一个样板核心和一个合成核心.它必须完全填满,不能是空心的.当装配机矩阵正确形成并供能后,框架上的线条会变成蓝色.\\n&7[A valid Assembler Matrix must contain at least one pattern core and craft core. It must be completely filled and can't be hollow. When the Assembler Matrix is correctly formed and powered, the lines on the frame will turn blue.]&f"
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"在这个例子中,我们将制作一个7x7x7的装配机矩阵,主要侧重于合成核心和样板核心之间的平衡.\\n&7[In this example, we will be making a 7x7x7 Assembler Matrix, focused mainly on balance between craft and pattern cores.]&f"
		""
		"制作前43个装配机&a矩阵框架&f和前125个装配机矩阵墙.我会在本任务的奖励中赠送每种25个(以达到总共68个框架和150个墙)\\n&7[Make the first 43 Assembler Matrix Frames and the first 125 Assembler Matrix Walls. I'll give 25 of each as a gift in the rewards for this quest (to reach a total of 68 frames and 150 walls)]&f"
	]
	quest.7900A4836CC55428.quest_subtitle: "一个频道容纳多个&a分子装配室&f和样板供应器&7[Many Molecular Assemblers and Pattern Providers in One Channel]&f"
	quest.7900A4836CC55428.title: "一体多机:&a装配机&f矩阵&7[Many Assemblers In One: The Assembler Matrix]&f"
	task.13FF4A021BBF1451.title: "无限单元&7[Infinity Cells]&f"
	task.1B927BD83D40F37D.title: "非熵金物品&7[Non-Entro Things]&f"
	task.3A76350DDF5A318D.title: "高级样板供应器&7[Advanced Pattern Providers]&f"
	task.3E8E72F0861329B6.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.475B673DC78361D2.title: "扩展设备&7[Extended Devices]&f"
	quest.0B1DF8A040826D87.quest_desc: ["现在你有了&c罗西奈特&r,你可以将其与&a蓝锥矿&r混合来制造&d因萨奈特&r锭.\\n\\n&a蓝锥矿&r可以通过&d工业先锋&f的矿石激光获得.\\n&7[Now that you have Rossinite, you can mix it with Benitoite to create Insanite ingots.\\n\\nBenitoite can be obtained with the Ore Laser from Industrial Foregoing.]&f"]
	quest.0B1DF8A040826D87.title: "因萨奈特&7[Insanite]&f"
	quest.14E5349DD740D026.quest_desc: [
		"To insert fuel into the reactor, you'll need to pick one of the sides that has a Reactor Solid Access Port and pump in Uranium from an inventory.\\n\\nThe easiest way to do this is to use something like a Storage Drawer or even just a Chest with an Item Pipe connected at the top, like the image shown below.\\n"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/extremereactors/importexample.png width:150 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.14E5349DD740D026.title: "为我们的被动反应堆添加燃料&7[Fueling our Passive Reactor]&f"
	quest.186731580B14F9D2.quest_desc: ["要与我们的涡轮机交互,我们需要几个&6端口&r.\\n\\n&9&a流体端口&f&r用于输入&b蒸汽&r等蒸汽,或输出&9水&r等废气.因此,你的涡轮机需要两个.\\n\\n&c能量输出口&r用于提取能量,是完成多方块结构所必需的.\\n&7[To interact with our Turbine, we'll need several Ports.\\n\\nThe Fluid Port is used to insert vapors like Steam, or extract exhaust, like water. Because of this, you'll need two for your Turbine.\\n\\nThe Power Tap extracts power, and is required to complete the multiblock.]&f"]
	quest.186731580B14F9D2.title: "涡轮机端口&7[Turbine Ports]&f"
	quest.19DE6EBEA8219E8E.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&e版权所有&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非AllTheMods团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.2598273041353196.quest_desc: ["建造&a再处理器&r时,你至少需要一个&e收集器&r和一个&9废料注入器&r.\\n\\n&e再处理器收集器&r必须放置在结构底面的中心.\\n\\n&9废料注入器&r必须放在顶面的中心,这是你输入或注入&9&a蓝晶锭&f&r等废料的地方.\\n&7[When building the Reprocessor, you will need at least one Collector and Waste Injector.\\n\\nThe Reprocessor Collector must be placed in the center of the bottom face of the structure.\\n\\nThe Waste Injector must go in the center of the top face, which is where you'll pipe in or insert waste like Cyanite Ingots.]&f"]
	quest.2598273041353196.title: "导入废料&7[Importing Waste]&f"
	quest.25D4406CB86C8CBB.quest_desc: ["既然我们现在从反应堆收集了一些&9废料&r,部分进程要求你将获得的部分锭”流体化”.你知道这意味着什么吗？\\n\\n我们需要制造一个&a流体化器&r!主要部件是&a流体化器控制器&r.建造完成后,你可以右键点击它以打开界面.在这里,你可以打开或关闭它,查看内部情况以及当前能量等级.\\n&7[Now that we are collecting some waste from our reactor, part of the progression requires you to \"Fluidize\" some of the ingots you get. You know what that means?\\n\\nWe need to make a Fluidizer! The main component is the Fluidizer Controller. Once built, you can right-click on this to open up the interface. Here, you can turn it on or off, see what's inside, and the current power level.]&f"]
	quest.25D4406CB86C8CBB.title: "流体化器&7[The Fluidizer]&f"
	quest.2A20000FAEC2E16A.quest_desc: ["要从反应堆提取能量或物品,甚至输入燃料,你需要这些&c必需的&r方块.\\n\\n&c能量输出口&r为你提供了一种”接入”&9被动&r反应堆产生的能量的方式.你可以连接管道和线缆从中提取能量.\\n\\n&a访问端口&r是每个反应堆都必需的,它允许你向反应堆输入燃料,或提取废料.通常每个反应堆配备2个是个好主意,各司其职.\\n&7[To extract power or items from your reactor, or even input fuel, you'll need these required blocks.\\n\\nThe Power Tap provides a way for you to \"tap\" into the power that a passive reactor makes. You can attach pipes and cables to extract the power from it.\\n\\nThe Access Ports are required for every reactor, and allows you to both input fuel from the reactor, or extract waste. It's usually a good idea to have 2 per reactor, one for each job.]&f"]
	quest.2A20000FAEC2E16A.title: "与反应堆交互&7[Interacting with the Reactor]&f"
	quest.2AF31F1769085641.quest_desc: [
		"&a再处理器&r是一个3x3x7的多方块结构,有特定的规则来完成多方块建造.\\n&7[The Reprocessor is a 3x3x7 multiblock structure that has specific rules to complete the construction of the multiblock.]&f"
		""
		"这个多方块结构的核心是&a控制器&r,只要不在框架上,它可以放置在任何垂直面上.\\n&7[The heart of this multiblock is the Controller, and can be placed on any vertical face as long as it isn't on the frame.]&f"
	]
	quest.2D592669F4D41793.quest_desc: ["就像反应堆一样,框架必须由&d外壳&r建造,但墙壁可以用&9&a涡轮机玻璃&f&r代替!\\n&7[Just like the Reactor, the frame must be built out of Casings, but the walls can be Turbine Glass instead!]&f"]
	quest.2D592669F4D41793.title: "涡轮机构造&7[Turbine Construction]&f"
	quest.354086C858E10154.quest_desc: [
		"既然我们现在从我们的小反应堆获得了一些蓝晶,我们需要一种方法将这些废料再处理成有用的东西.\\n&7[Now that we have some Cyanite from our baby reactor, we'll want a way to reprocess that waste into something useful.]&f"
		""
		"为此,我们需要建造另一个多方块结构:&a再处理器&r.\\n&7[To do this, we'll need to build another multiblock: the Reprocessor.]&f"
		""
		"这需要大量蓝晶,所以开始囤货吧!你可能也想升级到更大的反应堆.\\n&7[This takes a lot of Cyanite, so start stocking up! You might want to upgrade to a bigger reactor as well. ]&f"
	]
	quest.354086C858E10154.title: "再处理我们的废料&7[Reprocessing our Waste]&f"
	quest.3C3FE45CEF5E242B.quest_desc: ["虽然其他&a再处理器部件&r在建造时有固定位置,但这三个部件只要不在框架上,可以放置在任何垂直面上!\\n\\n&c&a能量端口&f&r用于为多方块机器供能以处理废料.\\n\\n&9&a流体注入器&f端口&r用于注入所需的液体,这将取决于注入的废料类型.对于蓝晶,那就是水!\\n\\n&a输出端口&r用于输出再处理后的材料.你可以&a右击&f它手动取出材料,或者用管道输出以实现自动化.\\n&7[While the other Reprocessor Parts have a mandatory spot when building, these three parts can be placed on any vertical face as long as they aren't on the frame!\\n\\nThe Power Port is used to give power to the multiblock machine to process waste.\\n\\nThe Fluid Injector Port is used to inject the liquid needed, which will depend on the type of waste injected. For Cyanite, that means water!\\n\\nThe Output Port is used to output the reprocessed material. You can right click it to grab the material out by hand, or pipe it out for automation.]&f"]
	quest.3F9D553C9FA64F2A.quest_desc: ["反应堆是多方块结构,意味着你可以创建自定义尺寸!\\n\\n如果你使用&a基础反应堆部件&r,可以建造的最大反应堆尺寸是5x5x5.\\n\\n使用&e强化反应堆部件&r可以制造的&l最大&r反应堆尺寸是32x32x48.有很多变量会影响反应堆的总输出,所以一定要多实验!\\n\\n一些总体建议:\\n\\n反应堆越高,它能容纳和燃烧的燃料就越多,因为有更多的燃料棒,意味着总功率更高.这也意味着更高的&c燃烧率&r.\\n\\n反应堆越宽,效率越高,前提是你不向设计中添加更多燃料棒.这意味着总体消耗更少.\\n&7[Reactors are multi-block structures, meaning you can create your own custom size!\\n\\nIf you're using Basic Reactor Parts, the largest size reactor you can build is 5x5x5.\\n\\nThe lBiggest Reactor that you can make using Reinforced Reactor Parts is 32x32x48. There are a lot of variables that contribute to the overall output of a reactor, so make sure to experiment!\\n\\nSome overall tips:\\n\\nThe taller the reactor, the more fuel it can hold and burn because there are more fuel rods, meaning more overall power. This also means a higher burn rate.\\n\\nThe wider the reactor, the more efficient it is, as long as you don't add more fuel rods to the design. This means less consumption overall.]&f"]
	quest.3F9D553C9FA64F2A.title: "扩展我们的反应堆&7[Expanding Our Reactors]&f"
	quest.4415C9F8DA2D7E68.quest_desc: ["有了蓝晶,我们可以制造涡轮机的核心,&9涡轮机控制器&r.\\n\\n涡轮机也是多方块结构,就像反应堆一样!它们输入由&d主动冷却&r反应堆产生的&7蒸汽&r等蒸汽,以产生海量能量!我们还需要一些其他部件来建造我们的第一个涡轮机.\\n\\n注意:&a基本型涡轮机&f部件只能用于建造最大尺寸为5x5x10的涡轮机.要建造更大的涡轮机,必须使用&a&a加强型涡轮机&f部件&r.\\n&7[With Cyanite, we can create the heart of the Turbine, the Turbine Controller.\\n\\nTurbines are multi-block structures, just like Reactors! They input vapors like Steam made by Actively Cooled Reactors to create TONS of power! We'll need a few other pieces to be able to build our first one.\\n\\nNote: Basic Turbine parts can only be used to build a max size Turbine of 5x5x10. To build a bigger Turbine, you must use Reinforced Turbine Parts.]&f"]
	quest.4415C9F8DA2D7E68.title: "制造涡轮机&7[Making Turbines]&f"
	quest.4745152F6FF242B3.quest_desc: ["当反应堆燃烧燃料时,会产生&9废料&r或&d反应物&r,你也需要将其提取出来.这就是另一个&a固体访问端口&f的用途!确保将其设置为输出模式,然后用管道将其导入某种存储设备中.\\n&7[When the reactor burns up fuel, it creates waste or a Reactant that you'll also want to extract. That is what the other Solid Access Port is for! Make sure to set it to output, then pipe it into some type of storage.]&f"]
	quest.4745152F6FF242B3.quest_subtitle: "&a物尽其用&f 不想浪费什么的……&7[Waste Not Want Not or something....]&f"
	quest.4745152F6FF242B3.title: "处理废料&7[Dealing with Waste]&f"
	quest.476755275B948A5F.quest_desc: ["反应堆也可用于加热&b冷却剂&r(如水)以产生&b蒸汽&r,例如&b蒸汽&r.\\n\\n为此,你需要建造一个强化反应堆.其建造方式与你建造3x3x3反应堆相同,但所有部件都需要替换为&a强化反应堆部件&r.我还建议它比3x3x3更大.\\n\\n要输入冷却剂,你需要一个&9Forge &a流体端口&f&r.这将把水等任何流体导入反应堆.它也可用于导出反应堆中产生的蒸汽.\\n\\n如果你愿意,可以创建一个&a&d通用机械&f &a流体端口&f&r,将流体蒸汽转换为&d通用机械&f的气体蒸汽.\\n&7[Reactors can also be used to heat up coolants like water to create vapor, like Steam.\\n\\nTo do this, you'll need to build a reinforced reactor. This is built in the same way that you built your 3x3x3 reactor, but all of the parts will need to be Reinforced Reactor Parts instead. I'd also suggest on it being bigger than a 3x3x3.\\n\\nTo input a coolant, you'll need a Forge Fluid Port. This will port in any fluids like Water into the reactor. This will also be used to export the vapor created in the reactor.\\n\\nIf you want, you can create a Mekanism Fluid Port to convert the fluid Steam into the Mekanism gas Steam instead.]&f"]
	quest.476755275B948A5F.quest_subtitle: "为了制造蒸汽!!&7[To Make Steam!!]&f"
	quest.476755275B948A5F.title: "建造主动冷却反应堆&7[Building An Actively Cooled Reactor]&f"
	quest.4AD8363D7359A072.quest_desc: [
		"我们将建造可能的最小被动反应堆,即&93x3x3&r.任务要求正是建造一个所需的确切数量.\\n\\n建造时,首先用外壳建造一个3x3x3的框架.在底面的中间,你可以直接使用另一个&a反应堆外壳&f.你需要每个外墙上都有一个&9反应堆组件&r,例如主动能量输出口或&a固体访问端口&f.\\n&7[We're going to build the smallest passive reactor possible, the 3x3x3. The requirements for the quest are the exact amounts for what you'll need to build one.\\n\\nTo build this, you start by building a 3x3x3 frame made out of Casings. In the middle of the bottom face, you can just use another Reactor Casing. You'll want each outer wall to have a reactor component, like an Active Power Tap or Solid Access Port.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"你建造的每个反应堆都需要恰好1个&6&a反应堆控制器&f&r,通常放置在前墙的中间.接下来,我们在多方块结构的中心放置1个&a&a燃料棒&f&r,并在其正上方的顶面放置1个&e&a控制杆&f&r.\\n\\n你需要一种输入和输出废料的方法,这可以通过使用&9反应堆 &a固体访问端口&f&r来实现.对于这个建造,在左侧和右侧各放置一个.\\n\\n为了提取能量,我们将在后墙的中间放置&c主动能量输出口&r.放置完成后,反应堆应该就绪!现在你可以&a右击&f &a控制器&f来打开界面并启动它!\\n\\n注意:使用&a基础反应堆部件&r可以建造的最大反应堆是5x5x5.要建造更大的反应堆,你将需要&e强化反应堆部件&r.\\n&7[Every reactor you build will require exactly 1 Reactor Controller, which is usually put in the middle of the front wall. Next, we'll place 1 Fuel Rod in the center of the multiblock, and 1 Control Rod above it on the top face.\\n\\nYou will need a way to input and output waste, which is done by using Reactor Solid Access Ports. For this build, place one on the left side and one on the right.\\n\\nTo extract power, we'll place the Active Power Tap on the middle of the back wall. Once placed, the reactor should complete! You can now right click the Controller to open up the interface and turn it on!\\n\\nNote: The biggest reactor you can make using Basic Reactor Parts is 5x5x5. To build a larger reactor, you will need Reinforced Reactor Parts.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这是一个3x3x3反应堆的样子:\\n\\n&7[This is what a 3x3x3 reactor will look like:\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/extremereactors/3x3sample.png width:150 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.4AD8363D7359A072.quest_subtitle: "学习基础知识&7[Learning the Basics]&f"
	quest.4AD8363D7359A072.title: "&d我们的第一个反应堆&7[Our First Reactor]&f"
	quest.4B9E9497E44D0096.quest_desc: ["要建造反应堆,你需要从制作&6&a反应堆外壳&f&r开始.\\n\\n这些构成了反应堆的框架和墙壁,不过如果你想看到反应堆内部,墙壁可以用&9&a反应堆玻璃&f&r替换.\\n\\n供将来参考,当一个部件标注”基础”时,意味着它只能与其他基础部件一起使用.基础部件也只能用于建造较小的反应堆,因为它有特定的尺寸限制.请记住这一点!\\n&7[To build a reactor, you'll need to start by making Reactor Casings.\\n\\nThese make up the frame and walls of your reactor, although the walls can be replaced by Reactor Glass if you'd like to see inside of your reactor.\\n\\nFor future reference, when a part says \"Basic\", this means that it can only be used with other basic parts. The Basic parts can also only be used to build smaller reactors, as it has a certain size limit. Keep this in mind!]&f"]
	quest.4B9E9497E44D0096.title: "反应堆建造组件&7[Reactor Building Components]&f"
	quest.4ED36AA3766E842B.quest_desc: ["与其现在建造最小的涡轮机,不如根据你的&9反应堆&r设计来建造涡轮机.\\n\\n首先,你需要建造一个能够处理反应堆&9蒸汽生产率&r的涡轮机.为了从中获得最大功率,它还需要保持900RPM或1800RPM的转速.这需要对不同的线圈、叶片数量和涡轮机的整体尺寸进行大量实验!\\n\\n注意:要完成此任务,你需要创建一个任意尺寸的&d&a目标显示器&f&r.放置后,你可以右击屏幕并选择此任务作为要求,然后将能量输出到任务屏幕方块中以填充它并完成任务.\\n&7[Instead of building the smallest Turbine at this point, it's better to build a Turbine based off of the design of your Reactor.\\n\\nFor starters, you want to build a Turbine that can handle the Vapor Production Rate of your reactor. To get the most power out of it, it'll need to maintain either 900RPM or 1800RPM as well. This takes a lot of experimenting with different coils, # of blades, and overall size of the Turbine!\\n\\nNote: To complete this quest, you'll need to create a Task Screen of any size. Once placed, you can right-click the screen and select this quest as the requirement, then output power into the task screen block to fill it up and complete the quest.]&f"]
	quest.4ED36AA3766E842B.title: "&d&a涡轮机&f&7[The Turbine]&f"
	quest.4FA6BEA4E646B742.quest_desc: ["在我们开始建造反应堆之前,需要熔炼一些煤炭或木炭来制作&9&a石墨锭&f&r.\\n\\n石墨与铁结合,是制造反应堆的主要材料之一.\\n&7[Before we can start building our reactor, we'll need to smelt some Coal or Charcoal to create Graphite Ingots.\\n\\nGraphite, coupled with Iron, is one of the main materials when making a Reactor.]&f"]
	quest.4FA6BEA4E646B742.quest_subtitle: "硬化碳&7[Hardened Carbon]&f"
	quest.4FA6BEA4E646B742.title: "用于外壳的石墨&7[Graphite for Casings]&f"
	quest.501C6B7580453410.quest_desc: ["&a流体化器&r是一个可定制的多方块结构,最小尺寸为3x3x3.就像其他多方块结构一样,框架需要用外壳建造,而面可以用玻璃建造.\\n&7[The Fluidizer is a customizable multiblock that has a minimum size of 3x3x3. Just like the other multiblocks, the frame will need to be made out of Casings, while the faces can be made out of Glass.]&f"]
	quest.501C6B7580453410.title: "流体化器建造&7[Fluidizer Construction]&f"
	quest.55DCA040C84DCEF3.quest_desc: ["如果你想获得&a流体化器&r制造的产品,需要在其中一个面上安装一个&a输出端口&r.\\n\\n&a流体化器&r需要能量才能运行,因此需要一个&c&a能量端口&f&r来完成结构.\\n&7[If you want to get your hands on the product the Fluidizer makes, you'll need an Output Port on one of the faces.\\n\\nThe Fluidizer will need power to operate, so a Power Port is required to complete the structure.]&f"]
	quest.55DCA040C84DCEF3.title: "所需端口&7[Required Ports]&f"
	quest.5914D015D8543875.quest_desc: ["&a流体化器&r可以在3种模式之一中运行:固体到流体、将2种固体结合成一种流体,或将2种流体结合成一种新流体.这完全取决于你为多方块结构使用的&a注入器&r类型.\\n\\n例如,如果你想将&d蓝托尼姆&r转化为流体,可以使用1个&a固体注入器&r.\\n\\n如果你想将两种固体结合成新物质,你将使用2个&a固体注入器&r建造多方块结构.\\n\\n如果你想结合两种流体,你将使用2个&9&a流体注入器&f&r.\\n\\n这可能看起来令人困惑,但对进程很重要.例如,你需要先将磁铁矿在流体化器中转化为流体,然后将其与卢迪克赖特一起送入&a再处理器&r以制造里迪克赖特.\\n&7[The Fluidizer can operate in one of 3 modes: Solid to Fluid, Combining 2 Solids into a Fluid, or combining 2 Fluids into a new Fluid. This all depends on the type of Injectors you use for the multiblock.\\n\\nFor example, if you want to convert Blutonium into a fluid, you can use 1 Solid Injector.\\n\\nIf you want to combine two solids together into something new, you'll build the multiblock with 2 Solid Injectors.\\n\\nIf you want to combine two fluids, you'll use 2 Fluid Injectors.\\n\\nThis might seem confusing, but is important for progression. For example, you'll want to convert Magentite into a fluid in the Fluidizer first, then send it to a Reprocessor with Ludicrite to create Ridiculite.]&f"]
	quest.5914D015D8543875.title: "运行模式&7[Operational Modes]&f"
	quest.5A615BB74A5CD332.quest_desc: ["使用&a再处理器&r,我们可以结合迄今为止制造的所有材料来制作一些新锭.\\n\\n注意:你可能需要一个&9流体化器&r来完成此步骤!\\n&7[Using the Reprocessor, we can combine everything we've made so far to make a few new ingots.\\n\\nNote: You might need a Fluidizer to complete this step!]&f"]
	quest.5A615BB74A5CD332.title: "卢迪克赖特 \\ 里迪克赖特&7[Ludicrite \\\\ Ridiculite]&f"
	quest.5AD80D3242DD3F60.quest_desc: ["这是模组中最难获取的材料之一!\\n\\n这也是可用的最强大的涡轮机线圈!\\n&7[One of the hardest materials to get in the mod!\\n\\nThis is also the most powerful Turbine Coil available!]&f"]
	quest.5AD80D3242DD3F60.title: "&d狂质方块&7[Insanite Block]&f"
	quest.67AFCBCE7AAC3089.quest_desc: [
		"要让涡轮机旋转,我们需要这些&c必需&r组件:\\n\\n- &9转子轴承&r放置在涡轮机轴的一端.这可以在任何面上,但决定了轴从何处伸出.通常放置在底面的中心.\\n\\n- &e转子轴&r从一个转子轴承延伸到涡轮机的另一侧,一直延伸到单个涡轮机外壳方块,形成涡轮机的轴.\\n\\n- &9转子叶片&r使转子旋转.这些放置在转子轴上,长度可以是多个方块.每个叶片可以处理一定量的蒸汽,并根据反应堆的生产率决定需要多少叶片.\\n\\n这是一个涡轮机垂直轴设置的示例,顶部是铅制涡轮机线圈.\\n\\n&7[To get a Turbine spinning, we'll need these required components:\\n\\n- Rotor Bearings are placed at one end of the shaft of the turbine. This can be on any face, but dictates where the shaft extrude from. This is typically placed in the center of the bottom face.\\n\\n- Rotor Shafts extend from one Rotor Bearing to the opposite side of the turbine, all the way to a single Turbine Housing block, creating the shaft for the Turbine.\\n\\n- Rotor Blades make the rotor spin. These are placed onto the Rotor Shafts and can be multiple blocks in length. Each Blade can handle a certain amount of vapor, and determines how many are needed based on your reactor's production rates.\\n\\nHere is an example of a Vertical Shaft setup for a Turbine, with the Turbine Coil of Lead on the top.\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/extremereactors/maxbasicturbine.png width:100 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.67AFCBCE7AAC3089.title: "创建&a涡轮机&f轴&7[Creating The Turbine Shaft]&f"
	quest.69642A3618E86DED.quest_desc: [
		"To build the frame for the Reprocessor, you'll need a lot of Casings. This also means a lot of Cyanite.\\n\\nStart by building a hollow 3 block wide, 3 block deep, and 7 block tall structure. This is the frame.\\n\\nIf done right, you'll have an empty spot in the middle of the bottom and top face. For the vertical faces, you can either use Reprocessor Glass or one of the required Reprocessor parts like the Power Port, Controller, etc.\\n\\nIf you'd like to see an image of what the frame will look like, check out the next page!"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"再处理器多方块结构的框架.\\n\\n&7[The frame of the Reprocessor multiblock.\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/extremereactors/reprocessorframe.png width:100 height:175 align:1}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"一个完全建成的再处理器:\\n\\n&7[A fully built Reprocessor:\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/extremereactors/reprocessorfull.png width:100 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.69642A3618E86DED.title: "建造框架&7[Building The Frame]&f"
	quest.6ADDFD55AD0DF7D4.quest_desc: ["在&a再处理器&r中将&9里迪克赖特锭&r与&c罗西奈特&r结合,将产生&d因奈特锭&r.\\n\\n我们现在可以用这些来制作&d因奈特&r方块.\\n&7[Combining Ridiculite Ingots with Rossinite in a Reprocessor will create Inanite Ingots.\\n\\nWe can now use these to make a block of Inanite.]&f"]
	quest.6ADDFD55AD0DF7D4.title: "因奈特&7[Inanite]&f"
	quest.75AD0CEBC1335915.quest_desc: ["&d&a反应堆控制器&f&r是反应堆的核心.当反应堆形成后,你可以右击终端打开反应堆界面.\\n\\n根据它是&9被动冷却&r还是&e主动冷却&r反应堆,界面会有所不同.被动冷却反应堆通过燃烧燃料直接产生能量.主动冷却反应堆利用产生的热量蒸发冷却剂,然后将其送入涡轮机以产生能量.\\n\\n在被动反应堆的界面中,你可以查看和切换状态及废料弹出.你还会看到温度、反应堆产生的FE/t以及反应堆&a每刻&f燃烧的燃料量.\\n&7[The Reactor Controller is the heart of the reactor. When a reactor is formed, you can right-click the terminal to open up the reactor interface.\\n\\nDepending on if it is a Passively Cooled or an Actively Cooled reactor, the interface will change. Passively Cooled reactors are used to produce power directly by burning fuel. Actively Cooled Reactors use the heat created to vaporize the coolant, which is then sent into a Turbine to create power.\\n\\nIn the interface of a passive reactor, you can see and toggle the status and waste ejection. You'll also see the temps, how much FE/t the reactor is producing, and how much fuel the reactor is burning per tick.]&f"]
	quest.75AD0CEBC1335915.quest_subtitle: "反应堆的核心&7[The Heart of the Reactor]&f"
	quest.775D176081DD75F5.quest_desc: [
		"当涡轮机完全建成后,右击涡轮机&a控制器&f将显示涡轮机界面.\\n\\n在这里,你可以看到涡轮机的所有统计数据.将鼠标悬停在每一项上会告诉你更多信息.\\n\\n在左下角,你将有两个箭头来控制&9流量&r.这控制了有多少加热蒸汽被泵入涡轮机.要知道应该将其设置为多少,请以反应堆的&d蒸汽生产率&r作为起点.\\n&7[Right-clicking on a Turbine Controller when it is fully built will show you the Turbine Interface.\\n\\nHere, you can see all of the stats for the Turbine. Hovering over each will tell you more info about each one.\\n\\nOn the bottom left, you'll have 2 arrows to control the Flow Rate. This controls how much heated vapor is pumped into the Turbine. To know how much you should set this to, check your reactor's Vapor Production Rate as a starting point. ]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/extremereactors/turbineui.png width:200 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.7B4AAC741F0A6073.quest_desc: ["每个反应堆都需要&9&a反应堆控制棒&f&r和&9&a燃料棒&f&r.这些控制燃料如何插入反应堆.\\n\\n&a控制杆&f放置在反应堆的顶面.每个反应堆也可以有多个,但必须至少有一个.通常,你拥有的控制杆越多,反应堆可以使用的燃料就越多,燃烧得也越多.这可能意味着总功率更高,但代价是更高的燃烧率,具体取决于反应堆的设置.\\n\\n对于每个&a控制杆&f,你需要足够的&a燃料棒&f延伸到反应堆的底部.例如,如果你的反应堆高5格,你需要从每个&a控制杆&f延伸出3个&a燃料棒&f.\\n\\n如果你右击一个&a控制杆&f,可以通过插入或收回燃料棒来控制反应堆中燃烧的燃料量.棒伸得越远,燃烧的燃料就越少.\\n&7[Every reactor needs Reactor Control Rods and Fuel Rods. These control how fuel is inserted into the reactor.\\n\\nThe Control Rods are placed on the top face of the reactor. You can also have more than one per reactor, but you must have at least 1. Typically, the more you have, the more fuel the reactor can use and burn. That can mean more overall power, but at the cost of higher burn rates, depending on the setup of your reactor.\\n\\nFor every Control Rod, you'll need enough Fuel Rods to extend to the base of the reactor. For example, if your reactor is 5 blocks tall, you'll need 3 Fuel Rods extending from each Control Rod.\\n\\nIf you right-click on a Control Rod, you can control how much fuel is burned in the reactor by inserting or retracting the fuel rods. The further that you extend the rods, the less fuel that will be burned.]&f"]
	quest.7B4AAC741F0A6073.title: "&a反应堆控制棒&f&7[Reactor Control Rods]&f"
	quest.7C4D8AA107780795.quest_desc: ["使用&a流体化器&r,我们可以将&d蓝托尼姆&r与&e黄铀&r结合制成&2维德赖特&r.\\n\\n当在反应堆中用作燃料时,&2维德赖特&r会产生&c罗西奈特&r作为反应物.我们需要这个!\\n\\n要将&2维德赖特&r用作燃料,你需要为反应堆制作&c燃料注入端口&r.\\n\\n注意:你可能需要清空反应堆中当前的燃料,或为此目的建造一个新的反应堆.\\n&7[By using the Fluidizer, we can combine Blutonium with Yellorium to make Verderium.\\n\\nWhen used as fuel in a reactor, Verderium produces Rossinite as a reactant. We need this!\\n\\nTo use Verderium as a fuel, you'll need to make Fuel Injection Ports for your reactor.\\n\\nNote: You might need to empty out the fuel currently in your reactor, or make a new reactor for this purpose. ]&f"]
	quest.7C4D8AA107780795.title: "罗西奈特&7[Rossinite]&f"
	quest.7C4E4793DA887DE4.quest_desc: ["基于原版模组&e大型反应堆&r,&a&d极限反应堆&f&r允许你建造可定制的多方块反应堆!\\n\\n主要元素当然是铀.你需要这个以及大量的煤和铁来开始建造.\\n\\n如果你在途中迷失方向,请参考&a&a极端&f之书&r寻求帮助!\\n&7[Based off of the original mod Big Reactors, Extreme Reactors allows you to build customizable multiblock Reactors!\\n\\nThe main element is of course, Uranium. You'll need this and a lot of coal and iron to get building.\\n\\nIf you're ever lost along the way, refer to The Extreme Book for help! ]&f"]
	quest.7C4E4793DA887DE4.quest_subtitle: "它不能吃……相信我&7[It's not edible... trust me]&f"
	quest.7C4E4793DA887DE4.title: "欢迎来到&9&d极限反应堆&f&r!&7[Welcome to Extreme Reactors!]&f"
	quest.7E07C5A6FA6B6B1F.quest_desc: [
		"一旦你建造了一个功能齐全的&a再处理器&r,你就可以泵入能量、水和&9蓝托尼姆&r来制造&d蓝托尼姆&r.\\n&7[Once you've built a fully functional Reprocessor, you can pump in power, water, and Cyanite to create Blutonium.]&f"
		""
		"这可以用作反应堆的燃料,并产生自己的废料,称为&9磁铁矿&r.\\n&7[This can be used as a fuel for your reactor, and creates its own waste called Magentite. ]&f"
	]
	quest.7E07C5A6FA6B6B1F.title: "蓝托尼姆&7[Blutonium]&f"
	task.27D8027E1B88F02A.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.2905C4386A407A1E.title: "&a涡轮机&f界面&7[The Turbine Interface]&f"
	task.4851C74261B5FA25.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.04D0543FE2820F64.quest_desc: ["是时候种些线了!其中一些允许你直接种植,而另一些则为你提供可用于合成配方的替代品.\\n&7[Time to Grow some string! Some of these allow you to grow it directly, whilst others give you an alternative that works in recipes.]&f"]
	quest.04D0543FE2820F64.quest_subtitle: "谁还需要蜘蛛呢？&7[Who needs Spiders anyway?]&f"
	quest.04D0543FE2820F64.title: "亚麻线&7[Flax String]&f"
	quest.0500DA5C4D383DC6.quest_desc: ["通过杀死僵尸或筛泥土获得这些.\\n&7[Get these by killing zombies or sieving dirt.]&f"]
	quest.0500DA5C4D383DC6.quest_subtitle: "吃你的蔬菜&7[Eat your veggies]&f"
	quest.083309154A8974DA.quest_desc: ["最基本的改进\\n&7[The most basic of improvements]&f"]
	quest.083309154A8974DA.quest_subtitle: "小幅提升&7[A slight boost]&f"
	quest.083309154A8974DA.title: "镀金食物&7[Gilded Foods]&f"
	quest.0893EFCAC7031FEA.quest_desc: ["是时候烤蛋糕了,如果你已经准备好了牛奶和鸡蛋.\\n&7[Time to bake a cake, if you've got some milk and eggs ready.]&f"]
	quest.0893EFCAC7031FEA.quest_subtitle: "鱼与熊掌兼得&7[Have your Cake and Eat it too]&f"
	quest.0A1C2A7A8617D3E4.quest_subtitle: "速通玩家最爱&7[Speedrunners Love this Stuff]&f"
	quest.0A1C2A7A8617D3E4.title: "小麦&7[Wheat]&f"
	quest.0A7F53BFE6A4DFDC.quest_desc: ["厌倦了只看到你能制作的配方？有了这个,你可以查看如何制作游戏中的每一种食物.\\n&7[Tired of seeing only recipes you can make? With this you can view how to make every food in the game.]&f"]
	quest.0A7F53BFE6A4DFDC.quest_subtitle: "烹饪百科全书&7[The encyclopedia of cooking]&f"
	quest.0A7F53BFE6A4DFDC.title: "无过滤食谱书&7[No Filter Cookbook]&f"
	quest.0AC713AEEBCF2CD2.quest_desc: ["或者你也可以用MA……但谁会那么做呢？\\n&7[Or you can use MA...but who does that?]&f"]
	quest.0AC713AEEBCF2CD2.quest_subtitle: "人性化鸡蛋收集&7[Humane egg collection]&f"
	quest.0AC713AEEBCF2CD2.title: "鸡蛋自动化&7[Egg Automation]&f"
	quest.0CB4CF33BD96D730.quest_desc: ["丰饶农业允许你通过修改作物属性来提高收获!(任务即将推出)\\n&7[Productive Farming allows you to increase crop returns by modifying their stats! (Quests coming soon)]&f"]
	quest.0EFF1AA37772156B.quest_desc: ["这个方块为多方块厨房提供水源.\\n\\n它也可以通过管道或缆线抽水来提供无限水.\\n&7[This block provides water to the multi-block kitchen.\\n\\nIt can also provide infinite water by pumping water out via cables or pipes.]&f"]
	quest.0EFF1AA37772156B.quest_subtitle: "1个方块搞定!&7[1 Block does the trick!]&f"
	quest.0EFF1AA37772156B.title: "水槽 = 无限水&7[The Sink = Infinite Water]&f"
	quest.0FE88A567578C720.quest_desc: ["这些是超级食物,能提供多种增益效果,具体取决于苹果种类.\\n&7[These are superfoods that give a wide array of buffs, depending on the apple.]&f"]
	quest.0FE88A567578C720.quest_subtitle: "结晶苹果&7[Crystallized apples]&f"
	quest.12139F09C0F1361D.quest_desc: ["提高生长速度,与绿色肥料冲突.\\n&7[Increases speed of growth, conflicts with green fertilizer.]&f"]
	quest.12139F09C0F1361D.quest_subtitle: "丰饶蘑菇&7[Productive shrooms]&f"
	quest.13AFCD3B6F62B986.quest_desc: ["提供冰和雪的配方!\\n&7[Provides Ice and Snow recipes!]&f"]
	quest.13AFCD3B6F62B986.quest_subtitle: "冰,冰,宝贝!&7[Ice, Ice, Baby!]&f"
	quest.13AFCD3B6F62B986.title: "冰升级&7[Ice Upgrade]&f"
	quest.1515B32545F51266.quest_desc: ["允许你为炉灶连接能源.\\n&7[Allows you to attach power to the Stove.]&f"]
	quest.1515B32545F51266.title: "加热升级&7[Heating Upgrade]&f"
	quest.1697CC05D08B388D.quest_subtitle: "美味的 &a炸鸡&f!&7[Yummy Fried Chicken!]&f"
	quest.1697CC05D08B388D.title: "&a鸡&f 必须走&7[The Chickens Must Go]&f"
	quest.1827DEEA2DF1B144.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到食物与农业章节!\\n\\n在这里,你会发现种植和制作食物的不同方法!\\n&7[Welcome to the Food and Farming chapter!\\n\\nHere, you'll find different ways for you to grow and make food!]&f"]
	quest.1827DEEA2DF1B144.title: "食物与农业&7[Food and Farming]&f"
	quest.18EADBAFC932F864.quest_desc: ["要剪羊毛你需要剪刀,没有其他方法能获得羊毛……对吧？\\n&7[To shear Sheep you need Shears, you wouldn't get Wool any other way...right?]&f"]
	quest.18EADBAFC932F864.quest_subtitle: "和平主义者路线&7[Pacifist Run]&f"
	quest.18EADBAFC932F864.title: "是时候剪毛了&7[It's Clippin' Time]&f"
	quest.1B4A74D744F39516.quest_desc: ["破坏一些 &a橡树树叶&f.\\n&7[Break some Oak Leaves.]&f"]
	quest.1B4A74D744F39516.quest_subtitle: "任何工具都行(包括你的拳头)&7[Any tool works (including your fist)]&f"
	quest.1B4A74D744F39516.title: "破坏树叶&7[Break the Leaves]&f"
	quest.1D2EF12FD7FDD217.quest_desc: ["鸡会自然下蛋.我猜这不算真正意义上的自然……\\n\\n我猜鸡只是在…… &o做鸡蛋运动!!!&r.\\n&7[Chickens will lay these naturally. I guess it's not really considered naturally...\\n\\nI guess the chickens are just getting... Eggs-ercise!!!.]&f"]
	quest.1D2EF12FD7FDD217.quest_subtitle: "……还是说呢？&7[...or am I?]&f"
	quest.1D2EF12FD7FDD217.title: "我不会玩鸡蛋双关语&7[I'm not gonna make an Egg pun]&f"
	quest.1D48298525EEADC9.quest_desc: ["你应该已经拥有所需的一切了.\\n&7[You should have everything you need already.]&f"]
	quest.1D48298525EEADC9.quest_subtitle: "给我撒点糖!&7[Pour some Sugar on me!]&f"
	quest.1D48298525EEADC9.title: "你真甜&7[You're so sweet]&f"
	quest.1DCAA0310AA55F1C.quest_desc: ["但他通常5点就关门了,所以谁在乎呢？\\n&7[But he usually closes by 5, so who cares?]&f"]
	quest.1DCAA0310AA55F1C.quest_subtitle: "威利会感到自豪&7[Willy Would be Proud]&f"
	quest.1DCAA0310AA55F1C.title: "渔夫的开端&7[The Start of a Fisher]&f"
	quest.1E7A4F84CEDBE2AF.quest_desc: ["骨粉是提高产量的最基本方法.\\n&7[Bonemeal is the most basic way to amplify your returns.]&f"]
	quest.1E7A4F84CEDBE2AF.quest_subtitle: "得用上那些骨头&7[Gotta use those bones]&f"
	quest.1E7A4F84CEDBE2AF.title: "促进生长&7[Improving Growth]&f"
	quest.1F114EB0AAB86DB4.quest_desc: ["市场为你提供一个村民,如果你有足够的绿宝石,他可以卖给你任何东西.\\n\\n剧透:通常每件物品只要1个绿宝石,幸运的是,他们拥有”一切”.\\n&7[Markets provide you with a villager than can sell you anything if you have the right amount of emeralds.\\n\\nSpoiler: It's usually just 1 Emerald per item, luckily, they have EVERYTHING.]&f"]
	quest.1F114EB0AAB86DB4.quest_subtitle: "&a村民&f 有多种生成方式&7[The Villager has more than one way to Spawn]&f"
	quest.1F114EB0AAB86DB4.title: "购买农场物资&7[Purchasing Farm Supplies]&f"
	quest.2786D5AC19163524.quest_desc: ["这个方块能在你的多方块厨房中启用熔炼配方!\\n&7[This block enables smelting recipes in your kitchen multi-block!]&f"]
	quest.2786D5AC19163524.quest_subtitle: "无需计时器&7[No Timer Needed]&f"
	quest.2786D5AC19163524.title: "亲爱的,厨房里有个熔炉&7[Honey, there's a Furnace in the Kitchen]&f"
	quest.28C9EDBF6607E180.quest_desc: ["这个方块是多方块厨房的一部分.\\n\\n它会向你展示你背包中或厨房多方块存储的食物可以制作的所有配方.\\n\\n你终于可以在Minecraft里打造一个漂亮的厨房了.\\n&7[This block is part of a multi-block kitchen.\\n\\nThis will show you every recipe that is available to you with the food you have in your inventory, or stored in the kitchen multi-block.\\n\\nYou can finally create a nice kitchen in Minecraft.]&f"]
	quest.28C9EDBF6607E180.quest_subtitle: "贝蒂·怀特出生在 &a切片面包&f 之前&7[Betty White was born before Sliced Bread]&f"
	quest.28C9EDBF6607E180.title: "自切片面包以来最棒的东西&7[THE BEST THING SINCE SLICED BREAD]&f"
	quest.2E9C035EEE7E5C34.quest_desc: ["经典的拴绳.用它把动物带到你的农场区域.\\n\\n这和矿石不是一回事.\\n&7[The classic Lead. Use this to get animals into your farm area.\\n\\nThis isn't the same thing as the ore.]&f"]
	quest.2E9C035EEE7E5C34.quest_subtitle: "走吧,小狗狗&7[Get along little Doggy]&f"
	quest.2E9C035EEE7E5C34.title: "我们用老式方法来做这个&7[We're doing this the Old Fashioned way]&f"
	quest.2FBF54AC8273E8DF.quest_desc: ["&d林业&f 添加了许多新树木,每种都有自己的好东西.你可以通过破坏树叶来收获这些果实.\\n&7[Productive Trees adds lots of new trees that each have their own goodies. You can harvest these fruits by breaking the leaves.]&f"]
	quest.2FBF54AC8273E8DF.quest_subtitle: "果实,果实,还是果实&7[Fruits and fruits and fruits]&f"
	quest.2FBF54AC8273E8DF.title: "&d林业&f&7[Productive Trees]&f"
	quest.34F29677E6B5E40C.quest_desc: ["提高每次收获的产量,与红色肥料冲突.\\n&7[Increases output per harvest, conflicts with red fertilizer.]&f"]
	quest.34F29677E6B5E40C.quest_subtitle: "丰饶霉菌&7[Productive mold]&f"
	quest.361DFDB1E1352D6B.quest_desc: ["在水边找一些 &a拐杖糖&f.\\n&7[Find some Sugar Cane near some water.]&f"]
	quest.361DFDB1E1352D6B.title: "糖,糖&7[Sugar Sugar]&f"
	quest.37CA6F9F0226F10E.quest_desc: ["这个方块存储用于烹饪的物品.\\n\\n你也可以在上面放置其他厨房多方块物品,比如烤面包机和 &a罐中牛&f.\\n&7[This block stores items for cooking.\\n\\nYou can also place other kitchen multi-block items on it, like toasters and a Cow in a Jar.]&f"]
	quest.37CA6F9F0226F10E.quest_subtitle: "我们需要更多烹饪空间&7[We need more cooking space]&f"
	quest.37CA6F9F0226F10E.title: "需要更多烹饪空间？&7[Need more cooking space?]&f"
	quest.3EA883C0BB7BD38F.quest_desc: ["让我们收集一些羊毛吧!\\n&7[Let's gather some pieces of Wool!]&f"]
	quest.3EA883C0BB7BD38F.quest_subtitle: "谁的羊毛是……彩虹色的？&7[Whose Fleece was....Rainbow?]&f"
	quest.3EA883C0BB7BD38F.title: "玛丽有只小羊羔&7[Mary had a Little Lamb]&f"
	quest.43021923E220CF68.quest_desc: ["要把泥土耕成耕地,你需要一把锄.\\n&7[To till Dirt into Farmland you'll need a Hoe.]&f"]
	quest.43021923E220CF68.quest_subtitle: "等到你有了机器再做这个……&7[Wait until you get Machines for this...]&f"
	quest.43021923E220CF68.title: "&a种植盆&f&7[The Planter]&f"
	quest.45F83C2750F70F9B.quest_desc: ["来吧,把一本书放进熔炉里烧.\\n&7[Go ahead, put a Book in a Furnace and smelt it.]&f"]
	quest.45F83C2750F70F9B.quest_subtitle: "完全不会着火……&7[Totally won't catch on fire...]&f"
	quest.45F83C2750F70F9B.title: "用一本书打造厨房&7[Making a Kitchen, with a Book]&f"
	quest.460969C070B5C8E5.quest_desc: [
		"我会说合成它是最简单的……\\n&7[I'd say crafting it is easiest...]&f"
		"我们不必止步于此!\\n&7[We don't have to stop here!]&f"
	]
	quest.460969C070B5C8E5.quest_subtitle: "原版的极限……&7[The limit of Vanilla...]&f"
	quest.460969C070B5C8E5.title: "“诺切“苹果&7[\"Notch\" apple]&f"
	quest.47764EFC822E462A.quest_desc: ["这个方块会随时间产出牛奶,并为厨房多方块启用牛奶配方.\\n\\n要把牛装进罐子,先把罐子放在一个坑里.引诱牛掉进罐子上方的坑里,然后在牛身上放一个铁砧.\\n\\n我不知道这玻璃是什么做的,但它比我和鸡的关系还要牢固.\\n&7[This block produces milk over time, and enables milk recipes for the kitchen multi-block.\\n\\nTo get a cow in the jar, place the jar in a hole. Lure the cow to fall in said hole above the jar, then drop an anvil on it.\\n\\nI have no clue what this glass is made of, but it's stronger than my relationship with Chicken.]&f"]
	quest.47764EFC822E462A.quest_subtitle: "非凡的挤奶能力……狭小的生活空间&7[Phenomenal Milking Powers....Itty bitty living space]&f"
	quest.47764EFC822E462A.title: "A &a罐中牛&f&7[A Cow in a Jar]&f"
	quest.528304AA09EA8C23.quest_desc: ["把它们都抓住!\\n&7[Gotta catch em' all!]&f"]
	quest.528304AA09EA8C23.quest_subtitle: "钓上几天鱼&7[Fishing for days]&f"
	quest.528304AA09EA8C23.title: "去钓鱼&7[Gone Fishin]&f"
	quest.55C4824DAD905512.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 为 AllTheMods 整合包创作.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 AllTheMods 团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.58495CFBF4F20CE9.quest_desc: ["它的功能就像厨房柜台,只不过是在空中.\\n\\n而且你不能在上面放东西.\\n&7[This works just like the kitchen counter, except in the air.\\n\\nAnd you can't put things on top of it.]&f"]
	quest.58495CFBF4F20CE9.quest_subtitle: "这么多活动空间!&7[So much room for activities!]&f"
	quest.58495CFBF4F20CE9.title: "更多存储空间&7[Even More Storage]&f"
	quest.58D5BD3106BFD94A.quest_desc: ["合成下一版本的书.我向你保证,这是值得的.\\n\\n我甚至会还你一颗钻石.\\n&7[Craft the next version of the book. I promise you, it's worth it.\\n\\nI'll even give you a Diamond back.]&f"]
	quest.58D5BD3106BFD94A.quest_subtitle: "这绝对值得&7[This is totally worth it]&f"
	quest.58D5BD3106BFD94A.title: "用钻石的力量烹饪&7[Cooking with the power of Diamonds]&f"
	quest.60053279577A59C1.quest_desc: ["厌倦了跳跃时毁掉你的作物？那你走运了!可与其他两种类型一起使用.\\n&7[Tired of annihilating your crops when jumping? Well you're in luck! Usable with the other two types.]&f"]
	quest.60053279577A59C1.quest_subtitle: "丰饶黄金&7[Productive gold]&f"
	quest.63050A2CACD6ADC9.quest_subtitle: "还是说呢？&7[or is it?]&f"
	quest.63050A2CACD6ADC9.title: "顶级钓竿&7[A Maxed Rod]&f"
	quest.635620A03E3505BF.quest_desc: ["我不想问你是怎么弄到这些的.\\n&7[I don't wanna know how you got these.]&f"]
	quest.635620A03E3505BF.quest_subtitle: "但是……牛不能被剪毛……&7[But....Cows can't be sheared...]&f"
	quest.635620A03E3505BF.title: "皮革&7[Leather]&f"
	quest.659A903F97F93BE2.quest_subtitle: "快速又简单&7[Quick and Simple]&f"
	quest.659A903F97F93BE2.title: "生命之面包&7[The Bread of Life]&f"
	quest.72717D1135486D7F.quest_desc: ["让我们收集一些种子.\\n&7[Let's gather some seeds.]&f"]
	quest.72717D1135486D7F.quest_subtitle: "方块手 1,草方块 0&7[Block Hand 1, Block Grass 0]&f"
	quest.72717D1135486D7F.title: "空手打草&7[Punch the Grass]&f"
	quest.73B8A70240E6070E.quest_desc: ["找到一头牛,用桶 &a右击&f 它.\\n\\n说真的,为什么没有公牛？\\n&7[Find a Cow and Right Click it with a Bucket.\\n\\nSeriously, why no Bulls?]&f"]
	quest.73B8A70240E6070E.quest_subtitle: "为什么游戏里没有公牛？&7[Why aren't there Bulls in the game?]&f"
	quest.73B8A70240E6070E.title: "挤牛奶 - 获利&7[Milk a Cow - Profit]&f"
	quest.791AE62ACACBD5BA.quest_subtitle: "你会打开它,关上它,然后再打开它,只因为你无聊&7[You'll open it, close it, then open it again, just because you're bored]&f"
	quest.79DD2C115A5FC23B.quest_desc: ["每个等级提供一种新的正面效果.可以说这些相当OP……\\n&7[Each tier gives a new positive effect. Safe to say these are pretty OP...]&f"]
	quest.79DD2C115A5FC23B.quest_subtitle: "等级苹果&7[Tiered apples]&f"
	quest.79DD2C115A5FC23B.title: "MA苹果&7[MA Apples]&f"
	quest.7FB5AFB3A30830D4.quest_desc: ["种植这棵树苗以获得最基本的水果.\\n&7[Grow this sapling to gain access to the most basic of fruits.]&f"]
	quest.7FB5AFB3A30830D4.title: "来自树木的果实&7[Fruits from Trees]&f"
	task.003A07A0E816B302.title: "丰饶农业&7[Productive Farming]&f"
	task.1D8904E53906D972.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.2725700B5EA1CD75.title: "剪刀&7[Shears]&f"
	task.323A434E1AF54408.title: "锄&7[Hoes]&f"
	task.32791AD78C17C814.title: "农夫乐事工具&7[Farmer's Delight Tools]&f"
	task.3824DC29D8790DAB.title: "宝石苹果&7[Gem Apples]&f"
	task.3DA0D9582AEFCBCF.title: "&a亚麻种子&f&7[Flax Seeds]&f"
	task.5805158E69C05AED.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.669DEA201002793D.title: "冰箱&7[Fridges]&f"
	task.690D9E03BB024BCF.title: "ATM锭金属&7[ATM metal]&f"
	task.6DF92BBEC7E3EC10.title: "ATM锭食物&7[ATM food]&f"
	task.73E843FE4FCCEA33.title: "MA苹果&7[MA Apples]&f"
	task.78D7794707E4BD83.title: "作物&7[Crops]&f"
	task.7C686DA23151A0F3.title: "黄金食物&7[Golden food]&f"
	task.7F08D4E77359BF4A.title: "羊毛&7[Wool]&f"
	quest.02F2DF9D9DA7833A.quest_desc: ["为了获得我们的 &9&a腐化灵魂&f&r,我们需要进行一些 &5附魔&r!\\n\\n我们在寻找 &5灵魂掠夺附魔&r.它可以附在武器上,每次你杀死一个生物时,都有几率生成一个 &9&a腐化灵魂&f&r.\\n\\n然后可以杀死它们来获得物品.尽量快一点,因为它们喜欢飞走.\\n\\n也许它们知道你想杀它们？\\n&7[In order to get our Corrupt Souls we'll need to do some Enchanting! \\n\\nWe are looking for the Soul Looting Enchantment. It goes on Weapons, and everytime you kill a Mob it has a chance to spawn a Corrupt Soul. \\n\\nThese can then be killed to get them as Items. Try to do it quickly as they like to fly away. \\n\\nMaybe they know you want to kill them?]&f"]
	quest.02F2DF9D9DA7833A.title: "&5灵魂掠夺附魔&7[Soul Looting Enchantment]&f"
	quest.03C54B07106091DD.quest_desc: ["&c&a炉火棱晶&f&r 可能是这些仪式中最常用的物品.\\n\\n你需要4个 &c&a烈焰粉&f&r、2个 &8煤炭&r 和一个 &b&a神秘水晶&f&r 方块来制作它.别忘了 &3元素遗物&r!它可以与工具一起使用,熔炼它们破坏的物品:粗矿到锭、原木到木炭、沙子到玻璃.\\n\\n你也可以用它作为熔炉燃料,但效果有点差.这很蠢,因为它的名字暗示它会更好!\\n&7[Smelter Prism is probably the most used Item from these Rituals. \\n\\nYou'll need 4 Blaze Powder, 2 Coal, and a block of Arcane Crystal to make it. And don't forget the Elementarium Relic! It can be used with Tools to Smelt the Items that they break: Raw Ore to Ingots, Logs to Charcoal, Sand to Glass. \\n\\nYou can also use it for Furnace Fuel, but it kinda sucks. Which is dumb because the name suggests it would be better!]&f"]
	quest.03C54B07106091DD.title: "&c&a炉火棱晶&f&7[Smelter Prism]&f"
	quest.050CD33E92601651.quest_desc: [
		"&c&l等级 1&r 对你来说不够？那么,你需要升级它!\\n\\n将一个埃德尔木木板放入 &6&l熔铸炉&r 的中心槽,并在基座上放置4个 &b&a神秘水晶&f&r 和4个 &a刷怪笼碎片&f.\\n\\n用小锤敲击它,你的 &c&l等级 1&r 就会升级为 &3&l等级 2 &6熔铸炉&r!\\n\\n现在,新的仪式将可用,&6&l熔铸炉&r 可以容纳更多精华,并且你可以使用第二个遗物!\\n&7[lTier 1 not enough for you? Then, you'll need to upgrade it! \\n\\nPut an Edelwood Plank in the center Slot of the lForge and place 4 Arcane Crystals and 4 Spawner Scrap onto the Pedestals. \\n\\nSmack it with a Gavel and your lTier 1 will upgrade into a lTier 2 Forge! \\n\\nNow, new Rituals will be available, the lForge can hold more Essences, and you can use a second Relics!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_tier1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.050CD33E92601651.title: "&l&3等级 2 &6熔铸炉&7[lTier 2 Forge]&f"
	quest.07BEE6FEC14765DC.quest_desc: ["相当简单的配方,需要粘土、铁、粘液球等等……\\n\\n磁石最好去掠夺,模组在 &c&l&a下界&f&r 的 &a战利品池&f 中添加了这些,所以别合成,直接找一个!\\n\\n蜡是 &6&l禁忌 \\ 奥术&r 添加的新物品,由 &a蜂蜜瓶&f 和粘液球混合而成!\\n\\n你可以把它用在 &6&a暗黑石基座&f&r 上以获得 &7磁化基座&r,它们与漏斗(以及像管道这样的类漏斗物品)协同工作.\\n\\n你也可以把它用在靴子上,以增加物品能被拖入你背包的最近距离!\\n&7[Pretty simple recipe needing Clay, Iron, Slimeballs, and more... \\n\\nLodestones are best to loot for, Mods add these in Loot Pools all over lThe Nether so don't craft one just find one! \\n\\nWax is a new Item added by lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus which is a mix of Bottle of Honey and Slimeballs! \\n\\nYou can use it on a Darkstone Pedestal to get Magnetized Pedestals which work in hand with Hoppers (and Hopper like Items like Pipes). \\n\\nYou can also use it with Boots to increase how close Items can be to get dragged into your Inventory!]&f"]
	quest.092BB595F75D5536.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到&6&l禁忌 \\ 奥术&r!\\n\\n要启动这个模组,我们需要一些&a神秘水晶&f.去筛一些尘土吧.\\n&7[Welcome to lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus! \\n\\nTo start this Mod we'll need some Arcane Crystals. Go sieve some Dust.]&f"]
	quest.092BB595F75D5536.title: "&6&l禁忌 \\ 奥术&7[lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus]&f"
	quest.0AC8FE3B59D1B09D.quest_desc: ["&a量子捕捉器&f是一个用于移动生物非常有用的工具.\\n\\n只需&a右击&f一个生物来”捕捉”它们,然后再次&a右击&f释放它们.\\n\\n不过,你需要携带一定量的&b奥瑞尔能量&r才能使用它,这取决于生物的生命值.生命值越高,需要的&b奥瑞尔能量&r越多!不过释放生物是免费的,不消耗任何东西.\\n\\n哦,等等,我可能应该告诉你如何制作它!你需要一个&7&a量子核心&f&r,它由&7符文&r、&c&a洁净之尘&f&r和&8燧石&r合成!\\n\\n&a刷怪笼碎片&f是通过不用&a精准采集&f挖掘刷怪笼掉落的,所以会破坏刷怪笼.\\n&7[The Quantum Catcher is a very useful Tool for moving Mobs. \\n\\nSimply Right Click a Mob to \"catch\" them, then Right Click again to let them go. \\n\\nYou'll need a set amount of Aureal on you in order to use it though, this is dependent on the Health of the Mob. More Health, more Aureal needed! It won't cost anything to let Mobs go though, that's free. \\n\\nOh wait, I probably should tell you how to Craft it! You'll need a Quantum Core which is crafted with Runes, Mundabitur Dust, and Flint! \\n\\nThe Spawner Scraps are drops from Mining a Spawner without Silk Touch, so it'll break the Spawner.]&f"]
	quest.0FD638380EECFFBD.quest_desc: [
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_forge1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"要开始建造你的锻炉,请按此图案放置我们的&9&a磨制暗黑石&f&r、&6&a神秘磨制暗黑石&f&r和&6镀金&a雕纹磨制暗黑石&f&r.\\n&7[To start making your Forge, place down our Polished Darkstone, Arcane Polished Darkstone, and Gilded Chiseled Polished Darkstone in this pattern. ]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_forge2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"”接下来,将我们的&a锻造台&f放在内部的&6镀金&a雕纹磨制暗黑石&f&r上,并用&c&a洁净之尘&f&r敲击它,你就会得到&6&l&a赫菲斯托斯锻炉&f&r!\\n\\n最后,将我们的&6&a暗黑石基座&f&r放在外围8个&6镀金&a雕纹磨制暗黑石&f&r的顶部!”\\n&7[\"Next place our Smithing Table on the inner Gilded Chiseled Polished Darkstone and smack it with Mundabitur Dust, you'll get the lHephaestus Forge!\\n\\nLastly place our Darkstone Pedestals on top of the 8 outside Gilded Chiseled Polished Darkstone!\"]&f"
	]
	quest.0FD638380EECFFBD.title: "建造&6&l锻炉&7[Building the lForge]&f"
	quest.15849165CA8C00F9.quest_desc: [
		"这是最后一个也是最强大的&6&l锻炉&r,所以当然意味着它是最昂贵的!\\n\\n你需要2个&5&a暗黑下界之星&f&r,它们由4个&5黑曜石钢&r和一个&a下界之星&f合成.\\n\\n2个&a&d龙鳞&f&r,由&d&a末影龙&f&r死亡时掉落.\\n\\n4个&3&a幽匿催发体&f&r,由&3监守者&r掉落,或者可以在&a深暗之域&f中用精准采集获得.\\n\\n以及&2&a陨星块&f&r,它只需要9个&2&a陨星碎片&f&r!\\n\\n这允许容纳更多精华和……终局配方？我到底是从哪里弄到这个任务页的？\\n&7[The last most powerful lForge so of course that means it is the most expensive! \\n\\nYou'll need 2 Dark Nether Stars which are made from combining 4 Obsidiansteel and a Nether Star. \\n\\n2 Dragon Scales which are dropped when the Ender Dragon on death. \\n\\n4 Sculk Catalysts which are dropped from the Warden, or can be Silk-Touched in the Deep Dark. \\n\\nAnd Stellarite Block which are just 9 Stellarite Pieces! \\n\\nThis allows even more Essences and...end game recipes? Where did I even get this quest page from?]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_tier5.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.15849165CA8C00F9.title: "&l&9第5级 &6锻炉&7[lTier 5 Forge]&f"
	quest.185DBBDD252CBA0C.quest_desc: [
		"&6&l锻炉&r是&6&l禁忌\\奥术&r中最重要的方块!现在你已经建造了多方块结构,你可以破坏&6&l锻炉&r方块并移动它,尽管它只在多方块结构上才能工作.\\n\\n你需要用全部4种精华填满它:&b奥瑞尔&r、灵魂、&4血液&r和&a经验&r!\\n\\n然后,如果需要的话,放入遗物.\\n\\n之后,将配方中的中心物品放入&6&l锻炉&r的中间槽位,外围物品放在&6基座&r上.\\n&7[The lForge is the most important Block in lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus! Now that you made the Multiblock you can break the lForge block and move it, even though it only works while on the Mutliblock. \\n\\nYou'll need to fill it with all 4 Essences: Aureal, Souls, Blood, and Experience! \\n\\nThen, put in Relics if necessary. \\n\\nAfter that, put the center Item in the Recipe, in the middle Slot of the lForge, and the outer Items on the Pedestals.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_gui.png width:135 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_tier3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.185DBBDD252CBA0C.title: "&l&c第1级 &6锻炉&7[lTier 1 Forge]&f"
	quest.198E9E90CC9606C4.quest_desc: ["我们把物品放在了基座上,我们有了&b奥瑞尔&r、灵魂、&4血液&r和&a经验&r……但它怎么还没完成？为什么还没完成？\\n\\n为了真正完成&a魔法仪式&f,我们需要使用一把仪式槌!\\n\\n它像&a镐子&f一样工作,但它在完成仪式方面有使用次数限制,只需用它&a右击&f&6&l锻炉&r即可!\\n&7[We got our Items on Pedestals, we got our Aureal, Souls, Blood, and Experience... and it isn't finishing? Why isn't it finishing? \\n\\nIn order to actually finalize the Ritual we'll need to use a Gavel! \\n\\nIt works like a Pickaxe but it also has a limited amount of uses for finishing Rituals, just Right Click the lForge with it!]&f"]
	quest.198E9E90CC9606C4.title: "完成仪式&7[Finishing the Ritual]&f"
	quest.2002AB7D061007FA.quest_desc: ["&6&a工匠遗物&f&r可以用第3级&a赫菲斯托斯锻炉&f合成,使用烈焰金、烈焰燃烧器、一些黑曜石和熔融核心.\\n\\n在&l&b克里巴诺&r中使用时,它将允许你制造&5黑曜石钢&r.\\n\\n在&6&l锻炉&r中使用时,它会为你提供&a经验&r消耗的折扣!\\n&7[The Artisan Relic can be crafted with the tier 3 Hephaestus Forge, using Blazegold, a Blaze Burner, some obsidian and molten cores. \\n\\nWhen used in the lClibano it will allow you to make Obsidiansteel. \\n\\nWhen used in lForges it will give you a discount on Experience used!]&f"]
	quest.2002AB7D061007FA.title: "&6&a工匠遗物&f&7[Artisan Relic]&f"
	quest.230EEE4671B46D0C.quest_desc: ["&9暗黑石&r通常出现在地下深处.但是……这里没有地下.幸运的是,我们有鹅卵石生成器来为我们提供一些暗黑石.\\n\\n将&a巫水&f和熔岩放在方块生成器旁边,并在下方放置一个&a神秘水晶块&f.不过熔岩会被消耗掉.\\n\\n它是&6&l禁忌\\奥术&r中使用最多的方块,所有多方块结构都将使用它们作为基础.\\n确保获取一大堆!\\n&7[Darkstone normally appears deep underground. But...there is no underground here. Luckily, we have Cobblegen Galore to provide some Darkstone for us. \\n\\nPlace Witch Water and Lava next to the Block Generator, with an Arcane Crystal Block underneath. The lava will be consumed though. \\n\\nIt is the most used Block for lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus, all Multiblocks will use them for their base. \\nMake sure to grab a ton of them!]&f"]
	quest.230EEE4671B46D0C.title: "&9暗黑石&7[Darkstone]&f"
	quest.29434DB0CC2E30E6.quest_desc: ["结合&c&a洁净之尘&f&r、&b&a神秘水晶之尘&f&r、&8木炭&r和一个&e&a金锭&f&r,我们将得到我们的第一种合金!&6&a圣金锭&f&r!\\n\\n这是&6&l禁忌\\奥术&r的基础锭,你将需要几十个!\\n\\n它尤其用于我们&a结构&f的建筑方块.\\n&7[Combining Mundabitur Dust, Arcane Crystal Dust, Charcoal, and a Gold Ingot we'll get our first Alloy! The Deorum Ingot! \\n\\nThis is the foundational Ingot of lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus, you will need dozens of it! \\n\\nIt is especially used for Building Blocks for our Multiblock Machines.]&f"]
	quest.29434DB0CC2E30E6.title: "&6圣金&7[Deorum]&f"
	quest.2ADA491A2485061C.quest_desc: [
		"&a经验&r是&6&l锻炉&r所需的第4个槽位和材料.\\n\\n要添加&a经验&r,你需要将以下3种物品之一放入&a经验槽&r.\\n\\n1. &a&a石化经验球&f&r,这些提供最多的&a经验&r.\\n\\n2. &a附魔之瓶&r,提供少量&a经验&r但容易获得!\\n\\n3. &5附魔物品&r,&6&l锻炉&r会将其&5附魔&r剥离并保留为&a经验&r!\\n&7[Experience is the 4th Slot and material needed for the lForge. \\n\\nTo add in Experience you'll need to put 1 of 3 things into the Experience Slot. \\n\\n1. Xpetrified Orbs, these give the most EXP. \\n\\n2. Bottle 'O Enchanting, gives a little bit of EXP but easy to get! \\n\\n3. Enchanted Item, the lForge will scrap the Enchantments off of it keeping it as EXP!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_experience.png width:135 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.2ADA491A2485061C.title: "&a经验&7[Experience]&f"
	quest.2D3C8905B783A212.quest_desc: ["用一些&a生物资源&f加上&b&a神秘水晶之尘&f&r,你可以制作&c&a洁净之尘&f&r!\\n\\n这是在合成和建造多方块结构时非常重要的一部分!\\n\\n你可以在&d&a末地城&f&r中找到它,大多数人最终都会这么做……\\n&7[For a few Mob Drops plus Arcane Crystal Dust you can make Mundabitur Dust! \\n\\nThis is a very important part in crafting and making of Multiblocks! \\n\\nAnd you can find it in End Cities which most just end up doing...]&f"]
	quest.2D3C8905B783A212.title: "&c&a洁净之尘&f&7[Mundabitur Dust]&f"
	quest.31AD9826FB036C98.quest_desc: ["&7符文&r可以被来自&d神秘学&f的任何矿工之灵开采!\\n\\n它们比&2星辉石&r更有用,但不如&b&a神秘水晶&f&r有用.\\n&7[Runes can be mined by any miner spirit from Occultism! \\n\\nThey're more useful than Stellarite but less useful than Arcane Crystals.]&f"]
	quest.31AD9826FB036C98.quest_subtitle: "这些以前是&5紫色&r的!&7[These used to be Purple!]&f"
	quest.31AD9826FB036C98.title: "&7符文&7[Runes]&f"
	quest.356102D5B5F3CA1E.quest_desc: ["&6&l禁忌\\奥术&r添加的一种合金是&5黑曜石钢&r.\\n\\n它在&l&b克里巴诺&r中制造,通过结合&a粗铁&f和&5黑曜石&r.\\n\\n你需要一个&a工匠遗物&f才能实际制造这种合金!\\n\\n另外,你会得到&6铜&r作为残留物,这可能不应该发生……\\n&7[An Alloy added by lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus is Obsidiansteel. \\n\\nIt's created in the lClibano, by combining Raw Iron and Obsidian. \\n\\nYou'll need an Artisan Relic in order to actually make the Alloy! \\n\\nAlso you'll get Copper as residue, which probably isn't supposed to happen...]&f"]
	quest.356102D5B5F3CA1E.title: "&5黑曜石钢&r&7[Obsidiansteel]&f"
	quest.3999AE0921641E60.quest_desc: [
		"&8&a暗物质&f&r通过烧炼埃德木获得.\\n\\n&5&a腐败之尘&f&r由&5黑曜石钢&r和一些&a生物资源&f制成.\\n\\n将这两者一起扔在地上,一个&8&a黑洞&f&r就会生成!\\n\\n&8&a黑洞&f&r会吞噬靠近的每个物品或弹射物,但我们想喂给它的是&a经验&r!\\n\\n当你喂给它足够的&a经验&r时,它会返还一个&a&a石化经验球&f&r.\\n&7[Dark Matter is created by Smelting Edelwood. \\n\\nCorrupti Dust is made with Obsidiansteel and some Mob Drops. \\n\\nThrow both these on the ground together and a Black Hole will spawn! \\n\\nThe Black Hole will void every Item or Projectile that comes near, but what we want to feed it is Experience! \\n\\nWhen you feed it enough EXP it will give back an Xpetrified Orb.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_blackhole.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.3999AE0921641E60.title: "&8&a黑洞&f&7[Black Hole]&f"
	quest.3BEE1B1DF87783A8.quest_desc: ["在这个整合包中,我们有第三种获取生长埃德木的方法.筛矿.用铁(或更好)的筛网筛一些苔藓,以获得那甜美可口的埃德木.\\n&7[We have a third way of getting Growing Edelwood in this pack. Sieving. Sieve some moss with an Iron (or better) Mesh for that sweet sweet Edelwood.]&f"]
	quest.3D82C6639A6371CB.quest_desc: ["4个&7&a量子核心&f&r和一个&c&a洁净之尘&f&r,你就可以得到&7量子注入器&r.\\n\\n&7量子注入器&r在这个阶段用得不多.我甚至不知道它们通常有什么作用,除了当你&a右击&f它们时会有一些花哨的动画.\\n&7[4 Quantum Cores and a Mundabitur Dust and you can get the Quantum Injector. \\n\\nQuantum Injectors aren't used much at this stage. I don't even know what they do normally, besides doing some fancy animation when you right click them.]&f"]
	quest.3D82C6639A6371CB.title: "&7量子注入器&r&7[Quantum Injector]&f"
	quest.40B757772D0FBAC9.quest_desc: [
		"&4血液&r是&6&l锻炉&r中需要填充的第3个槽位.\\n\\n你可以在&6&l锻炉&r上/附近杀死生物来添加&4血液&r.\\n\\n或者你可以存入装满的&a试管&f来将&4血液&r放入&6&l锻炉&r.\\n\\n要装满&a试管&f,请在杀死生物时将其放在副手.\\n&7[Blood is the 3rd Slot needing filling in the lForge. \\n\\nYou can either kill Mobs on/near the lForge in order to add Blood. \\n\\nOr you can deposit filled Test Tubes to put that Blood into the lForge. \\n\\nTo fill a Test Tube, have it in your Offhand when killing Mobs.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_blood.png width:135 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.40B757772D0FBAC9.title: "&4血液&7[Blood]&f"
	quest.414A35A72AFB5FF5.quest_desc: ["这个可能是最烦人的合成之一,它需要&b海晶石&r、&2海龟鳞甲&r、&9青金石&r和一个&3&a海洋之心&f&r.\\n\\n希望你喜欢&2&l神秘农业&r!\\n\\n它与头盔结合……很可能是为了提供水下呼吸或&a水亲和模块&f,但我无法让它工作……\\n&7[This one is probably one of the most annoying to craft, it needs Prismarine, Turtle Scute, Lapis, and a Heart of the Sea. \\n\\nHope you like lMA! \\n\\nIt combines with Helmets... most likely to give Respiration or Aqua Affinity, but I can't get it to work...]&f"]
	quest.414A35A72AFB5FF5.title: "&9&a海洋棱晶&f&7[Sea Prism]&f"
	quest.46567ED894E9883C.quest_desc: [
		"从这里开始就变得有趣了!\\n\\n使用4个&6圣金&r锭、4个&b&a神秘水晶&f&r和一个&9&a雕纹磨制暗黑石&f&r,从&3&l第2级&r升级到&e&l第3级&r.\\n\\n现在我们可以容纳更多精华、更多遗物和更多配方了!\\n&7[This is where it gets fun! \\n\\nUse 4 Deorum Ingots, 4 Arcane Crystals, and a Chiseled Polished Darkstone to upgrade from lTier 2 to lTier 3. \\n\\nNow we can hold even more Essences, even more Relics, and even more Recipes!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_tier2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.46567ED894E9883C.title: "&e&l第3级 &6锻炉&7[lTier 3 Forge]&f"
	quest.4707FB01F15F6E1F.quest_desc: [
		"&b&l克里巴诺&r是一个新的多方块结构,其作用有点像&a巨型熔炉&f!要制造它,请按照以下步骤操作!\\n&7[The lClibano is a new Multiblock which acts sort of like a Jumbo Furnace! To make it follow these steps!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_clibano1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"第一层是一个3x3的区域,角落由&9&a磨制暗黑石&f&r制成,其余部分用&9&a磨制暗黑石砖&f&r填充.\\n&7[First layer is a 3x3 Area, with the corners made of Polished Darkstone and the rest filled with Polished Darkstone Bricks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_clibano2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"&a第二&f层仅使用&9&a磨制暗黑石砖&f&r和&b&a炽炉核心&f&r.记得保持中间方块为空!\\n&7[The second layer uses only Polished Darkstone Bricks and the Clibano Core. Remember to keep the middle Block empty!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_clibano3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后一层和第一层一样……就在另外两层的上方!\\n&7[The final layer is just like the first... just above the other two layers!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_clibano4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后,用&c&a洁净之尘&f&r&a右击&f多方块结构来完成它!\\n&7[Finally Right Click the Multiblock with Mundabitur Dust to finish it!]&f"
	]
	quest.4707FB01F15F6E1F.title: "&b&l克里巴诺&7[lClibano]&f"
	quest.487C70679535DDDB.quest_desc: ["你不讨厌你的&a量子捕捉器&f上那些愚蠢的限制吗？不能把监守者放在你朋友的基地里!\\n\\n好吧,现在不用担心了,因为我们可以用3个&2&a陨星碎片&f&r和一个&a下界之星&f升级我们的&a量子捕捉器&f,制成Boss捕捉器.\\n\\n现在我们可以把Boss运送到任何我们想去的地方了!\\n&7[Don't you hate those stupid limitations on your Quantum Catcher? Can't put Wardens in your friends base! \\n\\nWell now there is no worries for we can upgrade our Quantum Catcher with 3 Stellarite Pieces and a Nether Star to make the Boss Catcher. \\n\\nNow we can transport our Bosses wherever we want!]&f"]
	quest.487C70679535DDDB.quest_subtitle: "我知道,三圣宝石,你不用对我大喊大叫&7[I know, Trinity Gem, you don't have to shout at me]&f"
	quest.49D0B6D3ED3DCCCD.quest_desc: ["&b&a神秘水晶之尘&f&r非常简单,只需烧炼&b&a神秘水晶&f&r,砰!\\n\\n你也可以使用克里巴诺多方块结构来回收一些&b&a神秘水晶&f&r!\\n&7[Arcane Crystal Dust is pretty simple, just Smelt Arcane Crystals and boom! \\n\\nYou can also use the Clibano Multiblock in order to get a few bits of Arcane Crystals back!]&f"]
	quest.49D0B6D3ED3DCCCD.title: "&b&a神秘水晶之尘&f&7[Arcane Crystal Dust]&f"
	quest.4A564E8FE587C7E4.quest_desc: ["获取灵魂的最佳方式是通过&a灵魂提取器&f!\\n\\n用一些下界物品和方块以及一个&a瓶罐&f(确实需要埃德木来制作),你就可以让你的工具具备灵魂搜寻能力!\\n\\n手持它&a右击&f&a灵魂沙&f,它会从中提取灵魂.\\n\\n&a留下&f它作为沙子……不,等等,是&a失魂沙&f……&a失魂沙&f到底是什么？!？!？!\\n&7[The best way of getting Souls is via the Soul Extractor! \\n\\nFor a few Nether Items and Blocks and an Utrem Jar (which does need Edelwood to craft) you can get your tool to Soul-Finding! \\n\\nHold Right Click with it on Soul Sand and it'll extract the Souls from it. \\n\\nLeaving it as Sand... no wait it is Soulless Sand... what the heck is Soulless Sand?!?!?!]&f"]
	quest.4BE209D5DAF1F321.quest_desc: [
		"&b奥瑞尔&r是&6&l锻炉&r中第一个也是最重要的槽位.\\n\\n你可以用&b&a神秘水晶方尖碑&f&r自动化它,或者存入&b&a辉光瓶&f&f/&b药水&r!\\n\\n你可以在大多数结构中的箱子里找到&b&a辉光瓶&f&r,或者用&b&a神秘水晶之尘&f&r和一个&a终极再生药水&f II来合成它们.\\n&7[Aureal is the first and most important Slot in the lForge. \\n\\nYou can either automate it with Arcane Crystal Obelisks or deposit Aureal Bottles/Potions! \\n\\nYou can either find Aureal Bottles in Chests in most Structures, or you can craft them with Arcane Crystal Dust and a Potion of Regeneration II.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_aureal.png width:135 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4BE209D5DAF1F321.title: "&b奥瑞尔&7[Aureal]&f"
	quest.4C93FCBAB7F3C00D.quest_desc: ["考虑到空岛世界里没有任何我们可以开采的矿石,你会认为我们会让你通过筛矿获得符文和星辉石,对吧？\\n错了!我们必须使用矿工之灵来获取它们.查看&d神秘学&f任务页面以了解更多关于该模组的信息.\\n&7[Given that there aren't any ores in a skyblock world that we can mine, you would think we would let you get Runes and Stellarite from sieving, right? \\nWRONG! We'll have to use Miner Spirits for them. Check the Occultism quest page to learn more about the mod.]&f"]
	quest.4C93FCBAB7F3C00D.quest_subtitle: "我以为这是禁忌奥术任务页面&7[I thought this was the Forbidden Arcanus Quest Page]&f"
	quest.4C93FCBAB7F3C00D.title: "&d神秘学&f?&7[Occultism?]&f"
	quest.4CFE097D0A8683C8.quest_desc: ["&a&5黑曜石&f头颅&r是一种头盔,佩戴时可以保护你免受火焰/熔岩伤害!\\n\\n随着时间的推移,它会磨损,你需要用&5黑曜石钢&r修复它.\\n\\n这也是你制作它的方法,一个&a骷髅头颅&f和8个&5黑曜石钢&r.\\n&7[The Obsidian Skull is a Helmet that when worn can protect you from Fire/Lava damage! \\n\\nOvertime it will wear down to which you'll need to repair it with Obsidiansteel. \\n\\nThat is also how you craft it, a Skeleton Skull with 8 Obsidiansteel.]&f"]
	quest.4CFE097D0A8683C8.title: "&5&a黑曜石头骨&f&7[Obsidian Skull]&f"
	quest.52472667678E10D1.quest_desc: ["&2星辉石&r生成在Y层……我为什么要说这个？你知道这里没有任何……我可能提到我们在空岛世界有点太多次了.\\n\\n你会想,有这么大的半径,应该很容易找到!但并不是,它非常稀有!如此稀有,只有玛里德和古神矿工才有足够熟练的技能找到它!\\n\\n不过开采时要小心,当它被破坏时会爆炸!\\n&7[Stellarite spawns between Y Level- why am I even saying this? You know there isn't any- I'm probably mentioning the fact that we are in a skyblock world a bit too much. \\n\\nYou'd think, with having such a huge radius it'll be easy to find! It isn't, it is very rare! So rare, that only Marid and Eldritch miners are skilled enough at being able to find it! \\n\\nBe careful when Mining it though, when broken it will EXPLODE!]&f"]
	quest.52472667678E10D1.title: "&2&a陨星碎片&f&7[Stellarite Pieces]&f"
	quest.52D4FCE72B15BC46.quest_desc: ["曾经想要一个”更好的桶”吗？那么你可以用&a埃德木桶&f!\\n\\n只需一些&a埃德木板&f,你就可以得到一个更好的桶,可以装4桶水或牛奶.\\n\\n你还可以装3桶熔岩!它更重,所以你只能装3桶而不是4桶.\\n&7[Ever want a \"better Bucket\"? Well you can with the Edelwood Bucket! \\n\\nFor just a few Edelwood Planks you can get a better Bucket, which can hold 4 Buckets of Water or Milk. \\n\\nYou can also hold 3 Buckets of Lava! It weighs more so you can only hold 3 instead of 4.]&f"]
	quest.539266A1C03C2EBA.quest_desc: [
		"灵魂是&6&l锻造炉&r所需的第二个槽位,也是最小的一个:只需要10个就能填满!\\n\\n每个灵魂和&a腐化灵魂&f都算作1个灵魂.而&a附魔灵魂&f则算作完整的10个!\\n&7[Souls is the 2nd Slot needed for the lForge, also the smallest one: only needing 10 to fill it! \\n\\nEach Soul and Corrupt Soul will count as 1 Soul. While Enchanted Souls count as the whole 10!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_souls.png width:135 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.539266A1C03C2EBA.title: "灵魂&7[Souls]&f"
	quest.53E2BEA626B35BFC.quest_desc: ["配方相当昂贵,但绝对物超所值!\\n\\n使用&6幽魂&4之眼&r会给予你&4&a幽灵视野&f效果&r.此效果会使半径100格范围内的所有生物获得&e发光&r效果!\\n\\n非常适合寻找地下的结构,或者&a混沌守卫&f召唤的&a守卫凋灵&f,甚至是你朋友隐藏的美西螈农场!\\n&7[Quite expensive recipe but most definitely worth it! \\n\\nUsing the Spectral Eye will give you the Spectral Vision Effect. This Effect gives Glowing to every Mob within a 100 Block radius in every direction! \\n\\nPerfect for finding structures underground, or Guardian Withers summoned by the Chaos Guardian, or even finding your friends hidden Axolotl farm!]&f"]
	quest.53E2BEA626B35BFC.quest_subtitle: "在ATM6中非常流行!&7[Very popular in ATM6!]&f"
	quest.53E2BEA626B35BFC.title: "&6幽魂&4之眼&7护符&7[Spectral Eye Amulet]&f"
	quest.580148D1141446A6.quest_desc: [
		"&c&l下界&r对你来说太可怕了？那么,你可以在&2&l主世界&r寻找灵魂!\\n\\n在你的世界中,你可能会发现一些游荡的迷失之魂.\\n\\n你可以杀死它们来获取掉落的灵魂!不过效率要低得多……\\n\\n&7[lNether too scary for you? Then, you can look for Souls in the lOverworld!\\n\\nWithin your World you might find some Lost Souls wandering around.\\n\\nYou can kill them for the Souls that they drop! It is much less efficient though...\\n]&f"
		"如果你在寻找灵魂方面遇到困难,你可能需要看看给你的剑附上灵魂掠夺附魔.用此附魔杀死生物偶尔会生成灵魂.\\n&7[If you are having troubles finding Souls, you might wanna look into Soul Looting enchantment on your sword. Killing mobs with this enchantment will occasionally spawn Souls.]&f"
	]
	quest.580148D1141446A6.title: "迷失之魂&7[Lost Souls]&f"
	quest.5A6FF0D4BA894306.quest_desc: ["&6&l禁忌魔艺&r的招牌物品,&a永恒陨星&r.\\n\\n用1个&b钻石&r、3个&a石化经验球&r和1个&2陨星碎片&r,我们可以制作出这个整合包中最强大的物品之一!\\n\\n你可以使用&a永恒陨星&r,配合一个物品和一个应用物品修饰符,来让物品失去其耐久度.不,等等,我的意思是让物品不再需要耐久度!基本上就是无法破坏的物品.\\n\\n这几乎可以用于所有有耐久度的物品,从&b钻石斧&r,到&a钓鱼竿&r,甚至&e强化荧石盔甲&r!\\n\\n有一些限制,它只对拥有耐久度而非使用次数(如&a注魔水晶&r)或能量(如Meka-Tool)的物品有效!\\n&7[The poster child of lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus, the 位阶l Stella. \\n\\nFor 1 Diamond, 3 Xpetrified Orbs, and a Stellarite Piece we can make one of the most overpowered Items in this Modpack! \\n\\nYou can use the 位阶l Stella with an Item and an Apply Item Modifier to make Items lose their Durability. No, wait I mean lose their need for Durability! Basically Indestructible Items. \\n\\nThis can be used on almost every Item with Durability from Diamond Axes, to Fishing Rods, to even Refined Glowstone Armor! \\n\\nThere are some limitations, it only works with Items with Durability not uses: like Infusion Crystals or Energy: like Meka-Tool!]&f"]
	quest.5A6FF0D4BA894306.title: "&a&a永恒陨星&f&7[位阶l Stella]&f"
	quest.5CD0E6F349F2F32D.quest_desc: ["别害怕,这不是什么吓人的东西,这是一棵完全成熟的埃德木!\\n\\n这棵树的顶部会有一个&a雕刻埃德木原木&r,并伸出&a埃德木树枝&r,这些可以被破坏以获得&a埃德木棒&r.\\n\\n原木内部是中空的,空间类似于一个炼药锅.有趣的是,它也能像炼药锅一样装水!\\n&7[Don't be afraid, this isn't an oogly boogly, it's a fully grown Edelwood! \\n\\nThe Tree will have a Carved Edelwood Log on top and Edelwood Branches coming from it, these can be broken for Edelwood Sticks. \\n\\nThe Logs are hollow on the inside, similar space as a Cauldron. Funny enough it can also hold Water like a Cauldron!]&f"]
	quest.5ED0DA95BAE43D88.quest_desc: ["最后一种棱晶,嗯,这个是&d水晶&r,但你懂我的意思!\\n\\n首先,你需要一个&e神圣契约&r圣物,它们可以在&b&l异界&r中找到.\\n\\n然后,你需要&3末影珍珠碎片&r、&5紫水晶&r和&a下界石英&r.别担心,后面会更难!\\n\\n现在我们需要每一种灵魂.我在其他任务中教过你如何获取灵魂和&9腐化灵魂&r,现在我来教你关于&d附魔灵魂&r的知识.\\n\\n在你的世界中找到一个四处飘荡的失落灵魂,然后朝它扔一瓶&b奥瑞尔喷溅药水&r!接着,它们会变成&d失落附魔灵魂&r,干掉它们!\\n\\n有了这些,你现在可以制作&d水晶&r了,它可以应用到工具和盔甲上,赋予其灵魂绑定效果.这意味着当你死亡时,你会在重生时保留这些物品在物品栏中.\\n&7[The last of the Prisms, well this one's a Crystal but you get the idea! \\n\\nFirst, you'll need a Divine Pact Relic, which are found in lThe Other. \\n\\nThen, you'll need Enderpearl Fragments, Amethyst, and Nether Quartz. Don't worry it gets harder! \\n\\nNow we'll need every type of Soul. I taught you how to get Souls and Corrupt Souls in other Quests now I'll teach you about Enchanted Souls. \\n\\nFind a Lost Soul flying around in your world, then toss a Splash Potion of Aureal at them! Then, they'll become a Lost Enchanted Soul, kill them! \\n\\nWith that you can now make the Crystal, which can be applied to Tools and Armor to give it Soulbound. This means when you die, you'll respawn with these Items in your Inventory still.]&f"]
	quest.5ED0DA95BAE43D88.title: "&d灵魂绑定水晶&7[Soul Binding Crystal]&f"
	quest.5F00A66CC1FE1F9F.quest_desc: ["说实话,这个配方唯一困难的部分是&a蝙蝠翼&r,你杀过多少次蝙蝠,更别说养殖它们了？\\n\\n这个物品相当新,并且不能与盔甲结合,它只用于游戏终局!\\n&7[Honestly the only difficult part of this recipe is the Bat Wing, how many times are you killing Bats let alone Farming them? \\n\\nThis one is pretty new and doesn't combine with Armor, it is only used for the end game!]&f"]
	quest.63C95FDAA447CA47.quest_desc: ["唯一需要&3&l二级&r的配方,&7撼地棱晶&r!\\n\\n你需要&7滴水石&r、&7滴水石&r和&8燧石&r,以及一个&b钻石块&r!\\n\\n像其他棱晶一样,制作它需要&3元素合金&r圣物.\\n像&c炽焰棱晶&r一样,&7撼地棱晶&r可以与工具一起使用.这些工具将能够以3x3区域挖掘,而不是只挖掘1个方块,它会挖掘9个!\\n&7[The only recipe which needs lTier 2, the Terrastomp Prism! \\n\\nYou'll need Dripstone, Dripstone, and Flint along with a Diamond Block! \\n\\nLike the other Prisms this will need Elementarium Relic in order to be made. \\nLike the Fiery Prism, the Terrastomp Prism can be used with Tools. These Tools will be able to mine in a 3x3 Area, instead of only 1 Block Mined it'll mine 9!]&f"]
	quest.63C95FDAA447CA47.title: "&7&a撼地棱晶&f&7[Terrastomp Prism]&f"
	quest.66FE4552E09B5EFF.quest_desc: ["棱晶对于许多&6&l禁忌魔艺&r的配方以及后续的其他模组都很重要!\\n\\n为了合成它们,我们需要&3元素合金&r,它由各种龙鳞在&a赫菲斯托斯锻炉&r中制成.\\n\\n我觉得告诉你哪里找不到它可能更容易些!\\n&7[Prisms are important for many of lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus recipes and other Mods later! \\n\\nIn order to craft them we'll need Elementarium, which is made with various dragon scales in the Hephaestus Forge. \\n\\nI think it would be easier to tell us where you can't find it!]&f"]
	quest.66FE4552E09B5EFF.title: "&3元素合金&7[Elementarium]&f"
	quest.67CCEFEBA4D79429.quest_desc: ["&e神圣契约&r是最难获得的,你需要为它们制作一些神圣手榴弹!\\n\\n它用于合成灵魂绑定水晶,以及……真的没别的了……\\n&7[Divine Pact is the most difficult to obtain, you'll need to make some holy hand grenades for them! \\n\\nIt's used to craft the Soul Binding Crystal and...nothing else really...]&f"]
	quest.67CCEFEBA4D79429.title: "&e&a神圣契约&f&7[Divine Pact]&f"
	quest.692183ACBB2AABF7.quest_desc: ["圣物是在你的&2&lMinecraft&r世界中罕见的发现!但是……在空岛世界里我们并没有战利品.幸运的是,你现在可以用&a赫菲斯托斯锻炉&r来合成它们了.\\n\\n它们可以在你的&6&l锻炉&r中使用,放在中心槽周围的格子里,你升级的等级越高,开放的格子就越多!\\n\\n或者你可以在&l&b克里巴诺&r中使用它们.\\n\\n有些是&a仅创造模式可用&r,别担心,我们知道你有多喜欢那些超强的物品,我们会研究添加它们的方法!\\n&7[Relics are rare finds around your lMinecraft World! But...we don't exactly have loot in a skyblock world. Luckily, you can craft them now with the Hephaestus Forge. \\n\\nThey can be used in your lForge, in the squares around the center slot, these open up more the more you upgrade the Tiers! \\n\\nOr you can use them in the lClibano. \\n\\nSome are Creative Mode only, don't worry we know how much you love your OP Items and will be looking into ways of adding them!]&f"]
	quest.692183ACBB2AABF7.title: "&l圣物&7[lRelics]&f"
	quest.6BA2BC09E23B34A9.quest_desc: [
		"这个需要另一个&9雕纹磨制暗黑石&r,但现在要加上4个&7符文&r和4个&2星辉石&r碎片.\\n\\n这个&6&l锻炉&r是基础&6&l禁忌魔艺&r的最后一个.\\n\\n当然,它包含了剩余的配方,而且现在所有圣物槽位都开放了!\\n&7[This one needs another Chiseled Polished Darkstone, just now with 4 Runes and 4 Stellarite Pieces. \\n\\nThis lForge is the last for the basic lForbidden \\\\ Arcanus. \\n\\nOf course it has the rest of the Recipes plus every space for Relics is open now!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/forbidden/forbidden_tier4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6BA2BC09E23B34A9.title: "&l&d四级 &6锻炉&7[lTier 4 Forge]&f"
	quest.6F57BE412A7BE84E.quest_desc: ["&9腐化灵魂&r有两种用途!\\n\\n1. 与&l&d四级 &6锻炉&r的合成配方有关,这个我们现在不用担心.\\n\\n2. 种植埃德木!\\n\\n种植埃德木充当埃德木的树苗,这是现在获取埃德木的唯一方式,除了筛矿.\\n&7[Corrupt Souls are used for 2 things! \\n\\n1. Crafting recipe with the lTier 4 Forge, which we don't need to worry about right now. \\n\\n2. Growing Edelwood! \\n\\nGrowing Edelwood acts as the Sapling for Edelwood, these are the only way of getting Edelwood now, alongside sieving.]&f"]
	quest.6F57BE412A7BE84E.title: "&9&a腐化灵魂&f&7[Corrupt Souls]&f"
	quest.7671AFAA1EFD287F.quest_desc: ["你想为你的&6&l锻炉&r慢慢自动化&b奥瑞尔&r吗？那么,你需要2个&b神秘水晶块&r、&6神秘磨制暗黑石&r和&c洁净之尘&r!\\n\\n放下&6神秘磨制暗黑石&r,然后在它上面放置两个&b神秘水晶块&r.\\n\\n一旦你建成了这个1x3x1的结构,用&c洁净之尘&r&a右击&r它来制作&b方尖碑&r!\\n\\n你可以将这些方尖碑放置在&6&l锻炉多方块结构&r中通常放置基座的位置,以自动化&b奥瑞尔&r!\\n&7[You want to slowly automate Aureal for your lForge? Then, you'll need 2 Arcane Crystal Blocks, Arcane Polished Darkstone, and Mundabitur Dust! \\n\\nPlace down the Arcane Polished Darkstone, then on top of it place both Arcane Crystal Blocks. \\n\\nOnce you get this 1x3x1 Structure, Right Click it with Mundabitur Dust to make the Obelisk! \\n\\nYou can place these, where the Pedestals usually go, in the lForge Multiblock in order to automate Aureal!]&f"]
	quest.7671AFAA1EFD287F.title: "&b&a神秘水晶方尖碑&f&7[Arcane Crystal Obelisk]&f"
	quest.79C9875A1A494762.quest_desc: ["如果你不想用&9腐化灵魂&r来种植埃德木,你可以依靠运气!\\n\\n&a悠闲&r商人有机会向你出售埃德木树苗,可以种植来生长埃德木.\\n\\n不过流浪商人非常随机,试着使用商人地毯来至少知道他会在哪里生成!\\n&7[If you'd rather not use Corrupt Souls to grow Edelwood, you can rest on Luck! \\n\\nThe Wandering Trader has a chance of selling Growing Edelwood to you, which can be planted to grow Edelwood. \\n\\nWandering Trader is very random though, try using Trader Carpets to atleast know where he'll spawn!]&f"]
	quest.79C9875A1A494762.quest_subtitle: "来自旺迪·T&7[From Wandy T']&f"
	quest.79C9875A1A494762.title: "购买埃德木&7[Buying Edelwood]&f"
	task.63D5DE02A5E407A1.title: "任意 #occultism:miners&7[Any #occultism:miners]&f"
	task.763964008982F4ED.title: "商人地毯&7[Trader Carpets]&f"
	quest.062AA943A1629A86.quest_desc: ["你把&z彩虹熔炉&r炸了？!？!就在它旁边点燃了TNT？你疯了吗？那花了那么多熔炉和资源,你居然把它炸了!!!你至少从里面得到了什么好东西吗？&z彩虹煤炭&r？能持续&m很久&r的煤炭？实际上那还挺值的.\\n&7[You blew up the zRainbow Furnace?!?! Just lit TNT right next to it? Are you mad? That took so many Furnaces and resources and you just blew it up!!! Did you atleast get something good from it? zRainbow Coal? Coal that lasts forever a long time? Actually that's pretty worth it.]&f"]
	quest.062AA943A1629A86.title: "&z&a彩虹煤炭&f&7[zRainbow Coal]&f"
	quest.07753C5D94312A50.quest_desc: [
		"&3增强&r:发电机是&3增强&r:工厂的反面,它不是消耗能量来熔炼,而是通过熔炼产生能量.你将不再在其中熔炼物品,所有使用的燃料都会被转化为能量!\\n&7[Augment: Generator is the opposite of the Augment: Factory, instead of using Energy to Smelt, it Smelts for Energy. You will no longer smelt items in it, every Fuel used will be made into Energy!]&f"
		""
		"(我在想,连接一个发电机和工厂熔炉,而不是只在一个熔炉里使用燃料,会不会更好)\\n&7[(I wonder if it's better to connect a Generator and Factory Furnaces instead of just using Fuel in one)]&f"
	]
	quest.07753C5D94312A50.title: "&3增强&r:发电机&7[Augment: Generator]&f"
	quest.0AD2B11565B484E7.quest_desc: ["你需要&5下界合金&r之前的所有熔炉.是的,所有,甚至&6铜&r!甚至&7银&r!甚至&3水晶&r!\\n&7[You'll need every Furnace before Netherite for these. Yes all, even the Copper! Even the Silver! Even the Crystal!]&f"]
	quest.0AD2B11565B484E7.title: "&z&a彩虹外壳&f&7[zRainbow Plating]&f"
	quest.0ADBE90B33ACC9FB.quest_desc: ["&z彩虹发电机&r在使用&3增强&r:发电机时,是对&z彩虹熔炉&r的增强.如果所有其他9个熔炉(不计入ATM熔炉及更高级的)围绕在&z彩虹熔炉&r周围,都装有&3增强&r:发电机,并且正在主动产生能量(有燃料且未满),它们将增强一个装有&3增强&r:发电机且正在工作的&z彩虹熔炉&r.它将额外产生每刻2kFE的能量!\\n&7[The zRainbow Generator is a boost to the zRainbow Furnace while using Augment: Generator. If all other 9 Furnaces (not counting AllTheModium Furnaces and above) are around the zRainbow Furnace, have Augment: Generator, and are actively making Energy (fueled up and not full) they will give a boost to a zRainbow Furnace that has Augment: Generator and is working. It will make 2kFE a tick more!]&f"]
	quest.0ADBE90B33ACC9FB.title: "&z彩虹发电机&7[zRainbow Generator]&f"
	quest.20EC8001A05CE2C8.quest_desc: ["无线热能是一种有趣且简单的为熔炉供能的方式.首先放置无线热能发射器并向其输入能量.然后将接收器放入发射器以绑定.最后将接收器放入熔炉的燃料槽以开始供能!\\n&7[Wireless Heat is a fun and easy way of powering Furnaces. First place the Wireless Heat Transmitter and put Energy into it. Then put the Receiver into the Transmitter to bind it. Finally put the Receiver into the Furnace Fuel section to start powering it!]&f"]
	quest.21EA29A8C7F950CE.quest_desc: ["&b钻石&r,&2Minecraft&r的支柱,显然也是升级熔炉的支柱……\\n \\n这些熔炉工作得更快,只需80刻或4&a秒&r来熔炼物品.这甚至比&a爆裂熔炉&r还快!\\n \\n这些只能由&e金熔炉&r合成,并且可以合成为&3水晶&r或&a绿宝石熔炉&r.\\n&7[Diamonds the staple of Minecraft, and of upgraded Furnaces apparently...\\n \\nThese work even faster only taking 80 Ticks or 4 Seconds to smelt items. That's even faster than a Blast Furnace! \\n \\nThese are only crafted by Gold Furnaces and can be crafted into Crystal or Emerald Furnaces.]&f"]
	quest.21EA29A8C7F950CE.title: "&b&a钻石熔炉&f&7[Diamond Furnace]&f"
	quest.2354BC5330350DF6.quest_desc: ["如果&a绿宝石&r不合你意,&3水晶熔炉&r可能正是你想要的!\\n \\n工作方式与&a绿宝石熔炉&r相同,为40刻.\\n \\n由&b钻石熔炉&r制成,并且可以制成&d黑曜石熔炉&r.\\n \\n(不,你看不到里面熔炼的物品,它只是透明的)\\n&7[If Emeralds aren't your thing the Crystal Furnace might be what you want! \\n \\nWorks the same as an Emerald Furnace at 40 Tick. \\n \\nMade with a Diamond Furnace and can be made into an Obsidian Furnace. \\n \\n(No you can't see the Items smelting inside it, it's just transparent)]&f"]
	quest.2354BC5330350DF6.title: "&3&a水晶熔炉&f&7[Crystal Furnace]&f"
	quest.25080E3295B1DF01.quest_desc: ["&5难得素熔炉&r熔炼物品的速度比整合包中任何其他熔炉都快!\\n&7[The 难得素 Furnace smelts items faster than any other Furnace in the pack!]&f"]
	quest.25080E3295B1DF01.title: "&5&a难得素熔炉&f&7[难得素 Furnace]&f"
	quest.2748ACEAB96A5F60.quest_desc: ["&d更多熔炉&r(不要与每个标题中的&l&d更多熔炉&r混淆,那是模组名和物品名)工作得比普通熔炉和&a铜熔炉&r更快.它们需要160刻来工作,或8秒.\\n\\n这些可以由普通熔炉或&6铜熔炉&r合成!并且它们可以制成&7银熔炉&r或&e金熔炉&r.\\n&7[Iron Furnaces (Don't be confused with each of the titles with lIron Furnaces being the mod name and an Item name) work even faster than Normal and Copper Furnaces. They take 160 Ticks to work, or 8 seconds.\\n\\nThese can be crafted from either a normal Furnace or Copper Furnace! And they can be made into either a Silver Furnace or Gold Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.2748ACEAB96A5F60.title: "&f&a铁熔炉&f&7[Iron Furnace]&f"
	quest.2E85D6E2CFCC356E.quest_desc: ["&3振金熔炉&r甚至比&6ATM熔炉&r更好!\\n&7[The 振金 Furnace is even better than the ATM Furnace!]&f"]
	quest.2E85D6E2CFCC356E.title: "&3&a振金熔炉&f&7[振金 Furnace]&f"
	quest.2EE8FCB63A338BC4.quest_desc: [
		"&z彩虹熔炉&r的合成几乎需要所有其他熔炉.8个&z彩虹外壳&r和1个&z彩虹核心&r给了我们所能想象的最好的熔炉!\\n&7[The zRainbow Furnace needs quite literally every other Furnace to Craft. 8 zRainbow Plating and 1 zRainbow Core gives us the best Furnace we could imagine!]&f"
		""
		"是的,它需要20刻或1秒来熔炼,但它不熔炼1个物品.你问多少个？一组物品有多少个？\\n&7[Yes it takes 20 Ticks to smelt or 1 Second to smelt, but it doesn't smelt 1 item. How many items you ask? How many are in a stack of items?]&f"
	]
	quest.2EE8FCB63A338BC4.title: "&z&a彩虹熔炉&f&7[zRainbow Furnace]&f"
	quest.32C7D8AE859BF89E.quest_desc: [
		"它可能是&d黑曜石&r,但别担心,你不需要&b钻石镐&r来拾取它,只是合成它需要.\\n&7[It may be Obsidian but don't worry you don't need a Diamond Pickaxe to pick it up, just to craft it.]&f"
		""
		"它每20刻或每秒工作一次.是的,不是&a秒&r,就是秒.\\n&7[It works every 20 Ticks or every Second. Yeah not Seconds just Second.]&f"
		""
		"它可以用&3水晶熔炉&r或&a绿宝石熔炉&r合成,并且可以制成&5下界合金熔炉&r!\\n&7[It can be crafted with a Crystal Furnace or Emerald Furnace, and can be crafted into a Netherite Furnace!]&f"
	]
	quest.32C7D8AE859BF89E.title: "&d&a黑曜石熔炉&f&7[Obsidian Furnace]&f"
	quest.33436ED0D9F128BD.quest_desc: ["&4增强&r:烟熏将你的&a铁熔炉&r变成铁烟熏炉.现在它只会烟熏食物物品,但速度快两倍!像&4增强&r:高炉一样,这个也可以与其他升级叠加!\\n&7[Augment: Smoking transforms your Iron Furnace into an Iron Smoker. Now it will only smoke Food items but twice as fast! Like Augment: Blasting this one also stacks with other upgrades!]&f"]
	quest.33436ED0D9F128BD.title: "&4增强&r:烟熏&7[Augment: Smoking]&f"
	quest.39605F1FEB1A5A1C.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods 工作人员&r或&2社区贡献者&r为用于AllTheMods整合包而创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下,未经&6AllTheMods 团队&r明确许可,此任务不允许在任何非&6AllTheMods 团队&r发布的公开整合包中使用.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.39605F1FEB1A5A1C.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.3A4C17878FC8315B.quest_desc: ["&6ATM熔炉&r与&a下界合金熔炉&r几乎相同.你需要它来合成&3振金熔炉&r.\\n&7[The ATM Furnace is pretty much the same as the Netherite Furnace. You will need this to craft the 振金 Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.3A4C17878FC8315B.title: "&6ATM熔炉&r&7[ATM Furnace]&f"
	quest.420FE84DEE12CCE0.quest_desc: ["&e金熔炉&r比铁熔炉更好,烹饪时间为120刻.\\n\\n它可以用&7银&r或&a铁熔炉&r合成,并且可以制成&b钻石熔炉&r!\\n&7[The Gold Furnace is better than the Iron ones with a Cooktime of 120 Ticks.\\n\\nIt can be crafted with Silver or Iron Furnace and is crafted into a Diamond one!]&f"]
	quest.420FE84DEE12CCE0.title: "&e&a金熔炉&f&7[Golden Furnace]&f"
	quest.49F08DE190AAD0D8.quest_desc: ["&3增强&r:工厂使你的熔炉更像&d通用机械&r中的熔炼工厂.它现在将使用能量而不是燃料!输入一些能量,它就会开始熔炼.\\n&7[Augment: Factory makes your Furnace more like the Smelting Factory from Mekanism. Instead of using Fuel it will now use Energy! Pipe in some Energy and it will start Smelting.]&f"]
	quest.49F08DE190AAD0D8.title: "&3增强&r:工厂&7[Augment: Factory]&f"
	quest.538821E23E39BE97.quest_desc: ["&2增强&r:&a燃料效率&r是为你们这些热爱地球、拥抱树木、拥护地球队长、嬉皮士的人准备的.&a熔炉&r消耗一半的燃料量,代价是时间减半.煤炭将不再熔炼8个物品,而是16个!\\n&7[Augment: Fuel Efficiency is for all you Earth-Loving, Tree-Hugging, Captain Planet Embracing, Hippies. The Furnace consumes half of the amount of Fuel at the cost of half the time. Coal will not Smelt 8 items but rather 16!]&f"]
	quest.538821E23E39BE97.title: "&2增强&r:&a燃料效率&r&7[Augment: Fuel Efficiency]&f"
	quest.553220A2CD7CAFE4.quest_desc: ["在圣诞节期间,所有箱子看起来都像礼物……但熔炉就像眼中钉一样突出!现在可以用&a包装纸&r来改变这一点!你可以&a右击&r将其应用到任何&l&a铁熔炉&r上,它就会为节日季做好准备!节日季过后,你可以按住Shift&a右击&r来拆开包装!\\n&7[During Christmas all the Chests look like Presents... but the Furnaces just stick out like a sore thumb! Now that can be changed with the Wrapping Paper! You can Right Click it onto any lIron Furnace and it'll be all set for the holiday season! And after the season is over you can Shift Right Click it to unwrap it!]&f"]
	quest.553220A2CD7CAFE4.quest_subtitle: "全部包装好&7[All Wrapped up]&f"
	quest.61847F47CCA225D9.quest_desc: ["遵循相同的模式,这些熔炉在140刻或7&a秒&r时熔炼.\\n\\n它们可以用&6铜&r或&d更多熔炉&r合成,并且可以用来合成&e金熔炉&r.\\n&7[Following the same pattern, these ones smelt at 140 Ticks or 7 Seconds.\\n\\nThey can be crafted with Copper or Iron Furnaces and can be used to craft a Gold Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.61847F47CCA225D9.title: "&a银熔炉&f&7[Silver Furnace]&f"
	quest.661C072E48F8D41F.quest_desc: [
		"&6铜&r如果不是最常见的矿石,也是其中之一,所以为什么不用一堆多余的&6铜&r来升级你的熔炉呢!\\n&7[Copper is one if not the most common Ore you can find, so why not use a bunch of spare Copper to upgrade your furnace!]&f"
		""
		"普通熔炉需要200刻来熔炼1个物品(20刻 = 1秒),而&6铜熔炉&r需要180刻.\\n&7[Normal Furnaces take 200 Ticks to smelt 1 Item, (20 Ticks = 1 Second) while Copper Furnaces take 180 Ticks.]&f"
		""
		"它们可以制成&7银&r或&f&d更多熔炉&r.\\n&7[They can be crafted into either Silver or Iron Furnaces.]&f"
	]
	quest.661C072E48F8D41F.title: "&6&a铜熔炉&f&7[Copper Furnace]&f"
	quest.686B25F2E9D8CC97.quest_desc: ["写这段话时正值七月底,所以距离万圣节还有大约3个月.但提前准备”惊悚”氛围永远不嫌早!就像Spirit Halloween商店一样,我们可以在万圣节实际开始前3个月就进入”惊悚”状态.这次的方法是,用&a右击&f一个熔炉来使用”惊悚转化器”!等到该为感恩节做准备时,按住Shift键&a右击&f它们来”解除惊悚转化”!\\n&7[At the time of writing this it's the end of July so I've got about 3 months until Halloween. But it's never to early to start getting Spooky! Just like Spirit Halloween we can get Spooky 3 months before it actually starts. This time by Right Clicking a Furnace with the Spook-alator! Once it's time to start getting ready for Thanksgiving Shift Right Click them to Un-Spook-Alate!]&f"]
	quest.686B25F2E9D8CC97.quest_subtitle: "”这就是万圣节”&7[\"This is Halloween\"]&f"
	quest.711DDD55CEC439E5.quest_desc: ["&a绿宝石熔炉&r,我在想村民会不会愿意交易它？\\n \\n它的工作速度是40游戏刻,或者说仅需2&a秒&f就能烧炼完成!一眨眼你可能就错过了.\\n \\n它们由&b&a钻石熔炉&f&r合成,并且可以升级为&d&a黑曜石熔炉&f&r.\\n&7[The Emerald Furnace, I wonder if Villagers will trade for it? \\n \\nIt works at 40 Ticks or only 2 Seconds to smelt! Blink and you might miss it. \\n \\nThese are crafted by Diamond Furnace and can be made into an Obsidian Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.711DDD55CEC439E5.title: "&a绿宝石熔炉&7[Emerald Furnace]&f"
	quest.73FF01D830A669AA.quest_desc: ["&4强化&r:爆裂将你的&a铁熔炉&f转变为铁制&a爆裂熔炉&f!它现在将只烧炼矿石,但速度翻倍!是的,这可以与其他强化效果以及不同等级的熔炉效果叠加.\\n&7[Augment: Blasting transforms your Iron Furnace to an Iron Blast Furnace! It will now only smelt Ores but at twice the speed! Yes this stacks with the effects of other Augments and different Tiers of Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.73FF01D830A669AA.title: "&4强化&r:爆裂&7[Augment: Blasting]&f"
	quest.757B14D08A9A03C4.quest_desc: ["和大多数模组机器一样,&d更多熔炉&f拥有配置功能.配置可以通过点击&a左上角&f找到.那里会有输入、输出和红石激活选项.&a红石&f激活决定了熔炉何时进行烧炼.顶部的按钮决定了它是否自动输入或输出,这意味着它会自动与连接的容器进行物品转移.那些方框代表熔炉的各个面,决定了该面是用于输入、输出、两者兼具、输入燃料,还是什么都不做.这对于管道输入/输出物品很重要.&a熔炉配置链接器&f可以将所有这些设置复制到其他熔炉上!\\n&7[ Like most Modded machines, Iron Furnaces has Configurations. Configs can be found by clicking the Top Left. There will be the Inputs, Outputs, and Redstone activation. The Redstone activation changes when the Furnace will smelt. The top buttons determine if it auto Inputs or Outputs, which means it will automatically move to and from connected Inventories. The boxes are each side of the Furnace and determine whether it Inputs, Outputs, does both, Inputs Fuel, or does nothing. This matters for Items being Piped in or out. The Furnace Settings Linker will copy all of these settings to other Furnaces!]&f"]
	quest.757B14D08A9A03C4.title: "配置&7[Configurations]&f"
	quest.78D1C97A542133D8.quest_desc: [
		"强化是对&a铁熔炉&f的升级!\\n&7[Augments are Upgrades to Iron Furnace Furnaces!]&f"
		""
		"在熔炉GUI的&a右上角&f,有一个按钮可以查看强化部分.那里会有红色、绿色和蓝色的槽位,每个槽位可以放置一个对应颜色的强化.\\n&7[In the Top Right of the Furnace GUI will be the button to look at the Augment Section. There will be a Red, Green, and Blue spot, each can hold 1 of their colored Augments. ]&f"
	]
	quest.78D1C97A542133D8.title: "&l强化&7[lAugments]&f"
	quest.79C4CF8D7312FC28.quest_desc: ["原版最佳!&5下界合金&r!别担心,你不需要&a锻造模板&f,只需要很多&5下界合金&r.\\n \\n它每5游戏刻烧炼一个物品,这意味着每秒可以烧炼4个物品.是的,现在不再是S.P.S.(秒/烧炼),而是S.P.S.(烧炼/&a秒&f).\\n \\n由&d&a黑曜石熔炉&f&r合成……等等,这还不是最终的熔炉？\\n&7[The best Vanilla gets! Netherite! Don't worry you won't need Smithing Template for it, just a lotta Netherite. \\n \\nIt smelts an item every 5 Ticks which means 4 Items Smelted every Second. Yes it's no longer S.P.S. (Seconds per Smelt) it's now S.P.S. (Smelts per Seconds). \\n \\nCrafted from Obsidian Furnace... wait this isn't the final Furnace?]&f"]
	quest.79C4CF8D7312FC28.title: "&5&a下界合金熔炉&f&r&7[Netherite Furnace]&f"
	quest.7A615E2A152917AD.quest_desc: ["为此你需要2个&5&a下界合金熔炉&f&r和7块玻璃,每块玻璃都是彩虹的一种颜色.&c红色&r、&6橙色&r、&e黄色&r、&2绿色&r、&3蓝色&r、&9靛蓝色&r- &5紫色&r,以及&5紫&r-&d品红色&r.没错!整个罗伊·G·比夫!\\n&7[For this you need 2 Netherite Furnaces and 7 pieces of glass which are each the color of the Rainbow. Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, Indig- Purple, and Vi-Magenta. Yep! The whole Roy G. Bpm!]&f"]
	quest.7A615E2A152917AD.title: "&z&a彩虹核心&f&7[zRainbow Core]&f"
	quest.7F67849DE9F700D8.quest_desc: ["&2强化&r:速度使你的熔炉更快!&b&a钻石熔炉&f&r将改为每40游戏刻烧炼一次,而不是80游戏刻.代价是燃料消耗翻倍.\\n&7[Augment: Speed makes it so your Furnace is faster! Diamond Furnace will instead smelt every 40 Ticks instead of 80 Ticks. At the cost of twice the Fuel usage.]&f"]
	quest.7F67849DE9F700D8.title: "&2强化&r:速度&7[Augment: Speed]&f"
	task.38B6F45109CB033A.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.5DB7A437BEC3E2D4.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.104EBBC08B4733F5.quest_desc: ["&d&a模拟室&f&r是HNN内的核心机器.\\n\\n当给予能量时,它将根据放置在内部的&b&a数据模型&f&r运行模拟.所需的能量也取决于放置在内部的&a数据模型&f,可以在模型的工具提示中看到.\\n\\n该机器还需要至少一个&9预测矩阵&r来运行模拟.\\n\\n模拟的结果将输出到矩阵上.模拟总会产生某种&e通用预测&r,可用于各种合成配方.它们也会根据&a数据模型&f中生物的来源而变化.\\n\\n如果模拟成功,你将获得一个基于该模型的&d生物预测&r.使用的&a数据模型&f等级越高,模拟的成功率就越高.\\n&7[The Simulation Chamber is the main machine within HNN.\\n\\nWhen given power, it will run simulations based on the Data Model that is placed inside. The power required also depends on the Data Model placed inside, and can be seen within the Model's tooltip. \\n\\nThe machine also requires at least one Prediction Matrix to run a simulation.\\n\\nThe result of the simulation will be output onto the Matrix. Simulations will always produce some kind of Generalized Prediction, which can be used in various crafting recipes. They also vary depending on the origin of the mob in the Data Model.\\n\\nIf the simulation succeeds, you will receive a Mob Prediction based off of the model. The higher the tier of the Data Model used, the higher the success rate is for a simulation.]&f"]
	quest.104EBBC08B4733F5.title: "&a模拟死亡&7[Simulating Deaths]&f"
	quest.10E8BC20D406D9FB.quest_subtitle: "制造各种下界材料&7[Makes various Nether Materials]&f"
	quest.12AE2856444996F6.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均采用&eAll Rights Reserved&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods Team&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods Team&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.14B3542ECB59869C.quest_desc: ["&5&a战利品制造器&f&r是让你从生物预测中获得甜美战利品的机器.\\n\\n当给予能量和一个成功的生物预测时,你将能够选择从该生物的&a数据模型&f中获取哪种物品.机器会记住你的选择,因此可以实现自动化.\\n\\n生物预测示例:\\n\\n- &d&a末影龙&f&r 对应 &d&a龙蛋&f\\n - &2僵尸&r 对应 铁\\n - &0凋灵&r 对应 &5&a下界之星&f\\n&7[The Loot Fabricator is the machine that gets you that sweet, sweet loot from Mob Predictions.\\n\\nWhen given power and a successful Mob Prediction, you will be able to choose which item you'd like to get from that mob's Data Model. The machine will remember your choice, so it can be automated.\\n\\nExamples of Mob Predictions:\\n\\n- Ender Dragons for Dragon Eggs\\n - Zombies for Iron\\n - Withers for Nether Stars]&f"]
	quest.14B3542ECB59869C.title: "制造&d战利品&7[Creating Loot]&f"
	quest.2559201BCF5D497C.quest_subtitle: "制造各种主世界材料&7[Makes various Overworld Materials]&f"
	quest.34CD54347E9821B5.quest_desc: ["一旦你制作了第一个&a数据模型&f,你需要将其升级才能发挥作用.\\n\\n&a数据模型&f从第一级开始:&7故障&r.如果你想在其上运行一些模拟,至少需要将其升级到&a基础&r!\\n\\n一旦放入&a深度学习机&f中,HUD会告诉你升级需要击杀多少生物.你也可以在模型本身的工具提示中看到此信息.\\n&7[Once you make your first Data Model, you'll need to level it up to be useful.\\n\\nData Models start out at the first tier: Faulty. You'll need to at least level it to Basic if you'd like to run some simulations on it!\\n\\nOnce placed inside of the Deep Learner, the HUD will tell you how many kills are required to level it up. You can also see this info in the tooltip of the Model itself.]&f"]
	quest.34CD54347E9821B5.title: "升级&a数据模型&f&7[Leveling Up Data Models]&f"
	quest.37EBB8E0D6E5F821.quest_desc: [
		"&6&d深度怪物学习&f&r(简称HNN)是一个围绕模拟生物击杀以获取战利品的模组!\\n\\n为此,你将收集生物的”数据\\n&7[Hostile Neural Networks (HNN for short) is a mod based around simulating mob kills for loot!\\n\\nTo do this, you will be collecting \"data\" on mobs, then running simulations from the data to create their drops!\\n]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/hnn.png width:150 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.37EBB8E0D6E5F821.title: "欢迎来到&9&d深度怪物学习&f&r!&7[Welcome to Hostile Neural Networks!]&f"
	quest.3E3CBDCEAB0FF28F.quest_desc: ["&9&a深度学习机&f&r是HNN的核心组件之一.\\n\\n使用此物品,你可以&a右击&f打开HUD并存储&6&a数据模型&f&r,以便在击杀生物时收集数据.\\n\\n每个学习器可以容纳4个&a数据模型&f,只要学习器在你物品栏的任何位置,它就会为放置在内的模型收集数据!\\n\\n注意:你可以在物品栏中拥有多个&a深度学习机&f,它会为所有学习器内的所有&a数据模型&f计数击杀数.\\n&7[The Deep Learner is one of the core components of HNN.\\n\\nWith this item, you can right click to open up a HUD and store Data Models to gather data while killing mobs.\\n\\nEach Learner can hold 4 Data Models, and as long as you have the Learner anywhere in your inventory, it will collect data for the models placed inside!\\n\\nNote: You can have multiple Deep Learners in your inventory, and it will count the kills for all Data Models inside all of the Learners.]&f"]
	quest.3E3CBDCEAB0FF28F.quest_subtitle: "&a唤知&f HUD&7[The Learning HUD]&f"
	quest.3E3CBDCEAB0FF28F.title: "&a学习生物&7[Learning Mobs]&f"
	quest.58C2ABED43B2EA61.quest_desc: ["&9模型框架&r是创建&a数据模型&f的起点.\\n\\n要开始收集特定生物的数据,你需要制作一个模型框架,然后&9&a右击&f&r你想要收集数据的生物.操作正确后,模型框架将变成你点击的生物的&a数据模型&f.\\n\\n要收集该生物的数据,将新创建的&a数据模型&f放入&a&a深度学习机&f&r中,然后开始用物品栏中的&a深度学习机&f击杀该特定生物.\\n&7[Model Frameworks are the starting point for creating Data Models.\\n\\nTo start collecting data on a specific mob, you'll want to make one of these then right click the mob you'd like to gather data on. When done properly, the Model Framework will turn into the Data Model of the mob you clicked on.\\n\\nTo gather data for that mob, place the newly created Data Model inside of a Deep Learner, then start killing that specific mob with the Deep Learner in your inventory.]&f"]
	quest.58C2ABED43B2EA61.quest_subtitle: "”收集数据”&7[\"Gathering Data\"]&f"
	quest.58C2ABED43B2EA61.title: "&9建模生物&7[Modeling Mobs]&f"
	quest.5A23107C363A209E.quest_subtitle: "制造各种末地材料&7[Makes various End Materials]&f"
	task.15D2A03410859443.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6B580F95A2E5A465.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.7F17E48ACE65C84E.title: "&a数据模型&f&7[Data Models]&f"
	quest.007A11C49E06F15F.quest_desc: ["这些可以合成.\\n\\n&9合成组件蓝图&r是最重要的&9蓝图&r之一.\\n\\n它用于帮助&6工程师装配台&r制造小型机械组件,比用工作台合成更便宜.\\n\\n它也可以用于合成独特物品,如&a灯泡草&f和电路!\\n&7[These can be Crafted. \\n\\nThe Crafting Component Blueprint is one of the most important Blueprints. \\n\\nIt is used to help the Engineer's Workbench make small Mechanical Components for cheaper than Crafting Tables. \\n\\nIt also can be used for Crafting unique Items like Light Bulbs and Circuits!]&f"]
	quest.007A11C49E06F15F.title: "&9&a转轮&f蓝图&7[Crafting Components Blueprints ]&f"
	quest.04DD3F761C210822.quest_desc: [
		"&c&l&a粗制高炉&f&r是我们生产&8钢&r的非常简单的(且粗糙的)方法.\\n\\n你需要喂给它一个&7&a铁锭&f&r和&0木炭&r或&0焦煤&r.\\n\\n每个&8&a钢锭&f&r需要烘烤60秒.&0木炭&r提供15秒,而&0焦煤&r提供完整的60秒.它们的方块形式也可以倍增这个时间.\\n\\n我们还会得到矿渣……它没什么用.\\n&7[The lCrude Blast Furnace is our very simple (and crude) way of producing Steel. \\n\\nYou'll need to feed it an Iron Ingot and either Charcoal or Coke. \\n\\nEach Steel Ingot takes 60 seconds to bake. Charcoal gives us 15 seconds while Coke gives us the whole 60 seconds. These can also be multiplied with their Block forms. \\n\\nWe also get Slag... it's pretty useless.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这是另一个3x3x3的结构,只不过这次用的是&c&a高炉砖&f&r.\\n&7[This one is another 3x3x3, just now with Blast Bricks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crude1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crude2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crude3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"又一次,我们用可靠的&6锤子&f&a右击&f前侧中间的那个方块!\\n&7[Another time where we Right Click the Front Middle Block with our trusty Hammer!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crude.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.04DD3F761C210822.title: "&l&c&a粗制高炉&f&7[lCrude Blast Furnace]&f"
	quest.063241B72BB3403E.quest_desc: ["&0&l&a重型盾牌&f&r的使用方式与普通盾牌一样,持握在副手并用它来防御.\\n&0&l&a重型盾牌&f&r确实拥有更高的耐久度,并能抵挡更多&a伤害&f.\\n\\n哦对了,它还有升级!这些升级可以通过&6工程师装配台&r添加.\\n\\n&a盾牌&f可以容纳2个升级.\\n&7[The lHeavy Plated Shield is used just like a normal Shield, hold it in your Offhand and use it to defend yourself. \\nThe lHeavy Plated Shield does have much more Durability and protects from more Damage. \\n\\nOh yeah it also has Upgrades! These upgrades can be added on with the Engineer's Workbench. \\n\\nThe Shield can hold 2 Upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.063241B72BB3403E.title: "&8&l&a重型盾牌&f&7[lHeavy Plated Shield]&f"
	quest.066B8A75B299AED8.quest_desc: [
		"&9&l挤压机&r是一台简单的机器,通过挤压&e物品&r来制造其他&e物品&r或&b流体&r.\\n\\n我们可以使用背面的2个端口来&9输入&e物品&r.然后我们需要使用桶&a右侧&f的端口来&6取出&e物品&r.该端口下方的端口将&6输出&b流体&r.\\n\\n这主要用于从&a作物种子&f(如&a小麦种子&f或&a大麻种子&f)中挤压出&a植物燃油&f!\\n\\n有些种子出油更多,查看&6指南&r了解每种种子能产出多少.\\n\\n我们还需要使用&9&l挤压机&r从8个&0&a焦煤粉&f&r中获取&0&a高定向热解石墨粉&f&r.\\n&7[The lSqueezer is a simple Machine that squeezes Items to make other Items or Fluids. \\n\\nWe can use the 2 Ports in the Back to Input Items. We'll then need to use the Port on the Right Side of the Barrels to take Items out. The Port below that one will Output Fluids. \\n\\nThis will mainly be used to squeeze Plant Oil out of Crop Seeds like Wheat Seeds or Hemp Seeds! \\n\\nSome Seeds give more Oil, check the Guide to see what each gives. \\n\\nWe'll also need to use the lSqueezer to get HOP Graphite Dust from 8 Coke Dust.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"字面意思上和&2&l发酵桶&r完全一样的开头.\\n&7[Literally the exact same start as the lFermenter.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_squeezer1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"也和&2&l发酵桶&r一样,只是用桶代替炼药锅!\\n&7[Just like the lFermenter as well, just instead of Cauldrons use Barrels!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_squeezer2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"在位于&e&a轻型工程块&f&r和&4&a红石工程块&f&r之间的桶上方放置一个活塞.在其他3个桶的顶部放置&8&a钢栅栏&f&r!\\n&7[Above the Barrel between the Light Engineering Block and Redstone Engineering Block place a Piston. On top of the other 3 Barrels place Steel Fence!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_squeezer3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"非常简单,用&6锤子&f&a右击&f活塞下方的桶.\\n&7[Very easy Hammer Right Click on the Barrel beneath the Piston.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_squeezer.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.066B8A75B299AED8.title: "&9&l挤压机&7[lSqueezer]&f"
	quest.0A7B0D0B81E138DE.quest_desc: ["&e&l工程师工具箱&r的作用类似于一个分区的潜影盒.\\n\\n它有分区:食物区,你只能放入食物.工具区,可以容纳&8&lIE&r工具或其他工具,但不能放&b桶&r.&c线缆&r区,可以放&c线缆&r、&c连接器&r或&c继电器&r.以及任意区,它不设限制.试着更像任意区一点!\\n\\n不过有些物品无法放入其中,比如&b装满流体的桶&r或&a蓄电池背包&f.\\n\\n你可以按住Shift键&a右击&f放置&e&l工具箱&r使其像箱子一样,然后用同样的方式拾取它.\\n&7[The lEngineer's Toolbox works as a segregated Shulker. \\n\\nIt has sections: Food, which you can only put Food in. Tools, which can hold lIE Tools or other Tools just not Buckets. Wiring, which can have Wires, Connectors, or Relays. And Anything, which doesn't discriminate. Try to be more like the Anything section! \\n\\nSome Items can't be held within it though, like Buckets full of Fluids or Accumulator Backpacks. \\n\\nYou can Shift Right Click to place down the lToolbox to make it act like a Chest, then you can do the same to pick it up.]&f"]
	quest.0A7B0D0B81E138DE.title: "&e&l工程师工具箱&7[lEngineer's Toolbox]&f"
	quest.0ACC0092A8F722C6.quest_desc: ["&8&lIE&r中的大多数机器都需要&c能量&r才能工作,而&c线缆&r就是我们传输能量的方式!\\n\\n&c线缆&r的附着方式是,用&c线缆卷&r&a右击&f一个部件,然后用同一个&c线缆卷&r&a右击&f第二个部件.它们的路径不能被阻挡,否则无法连接.\\n\\n要拾取&c线缆&r,我们可以破坏它们连接的东西,或者使用我们可靠的&6钢丝钳&r!\\n\\n不同等级的&c线缆&r影响其传输量,&5高压&r传输最多.\\n&7[Most Machines in lIE will need Energy to work, and Wires are how we move it! \\n\\nWires are attached by Right Clicking one part with the Wire Coil, then Right Clicking the second part with the same Coil. Their way can't be obstructed or else it won't connect. \\n\\nTo pick up Wires we can break what they are connected to, or use our trusty Wire Cutters! \\n\\nThe different Tiers of Wires effect how much they transfer, HV moving the most.]&f"]
	quest.0ACC0092A8F722C6.title: "&c线缆卷&7[Wire Coils]&f"
	quest.0AE6AD813928DE4F.quest_desc: ["&a外置加热器&f可以与熔炉一起使用,比如&2&l原版&r的熔炉,而不是&c&l&a粗制高炉&f&r!\\n\\n它从底部吸收&c能量&r并将其转化为热量.\\n\\n热量从它的其他侧面散发出来,传递到相邻的方块.\\n\\n从技术上讲,它用于&4&l&a强化高炉&f&r,通过制作预热器,但我不算那个!\\n&7[The External Heater can be used with Furnaces, like the lVanilla ones, not lCrude Blast Furnace! \\n\\nIt takes in Energy from the Bottom and uses it for Heat. \\n\\nThe Heat comes out of the other sides of it, to adjacent Blocks. \\n\\nIt is technically used for the lImproved Blast Furnace, by Crafting the Preheaters but I don't count that!]&f"]
	quest.0D212038C0A45E0B.quest_desc: ["&a卡苏尔弹&f是默认子弹.它们造成5颗心的&a伤害&f,仅此而已!\\n\\n&a穿甲弹&f有更高的几率无视&a护甲值&f.这对付像Bulwark这样的生物非常完美.\\n\\n霰弹不会发射1个弹丸,而是会发射多个弹丸.近距离使用效果最佳!\\n\\n&a银弹&f的作用类似于&a卡苏尔弹&f,但对亡灵生物(僵尸和骷髅)造成更高的&a伤害&f!\\n&7[Casull Cartridges are the default Bullets. They deal 5 Hearts of Damage, and that's it! \\n\\nArmor Piercing Cartridges will have a higher chance of ignoring Armor Points. This is perfect against Mobs like the Bulwark. \\n\\nBuckshot Shells will instead of shooting 1 Projectile, it will shoot multiple Projectiles. Use in close range for best effects! \\n\\nSilver Cartridges will act like Casull Cartridges but with higher Damage to the Undead Mobs: Zombies and Skeletons!]&f"]
	quest.0D212038C0A45E0B.title: "&a普通子弹&f&7[Common Projectiles]&f"
	quest.0D2D1F99945BA209.quest_desc: ["它本应在你双击S时装备你的&8&l&a重型盾牌&f&r……重点是”本应”.\\n\\n提醒一下,&8&lIE&r仍处于测试阶段!模组开发需要大量的时间和精力,请尊重这一点!\\n&7[It is supposed to Equip your lHeavy Plated Shield when you Double Tap S... emphasis on supposed to. \\n\\nReminder that lIE is in Beta still! Mod Development takes a lot of time and effort, be respectful of such!]&f"]
	quest.0F14270F0A718C01.quest_desc: ["&c岩浆&r - 1300 K \\n&c熔岩&r - 1300 K \\n&a铀&r - 2000 K\\n&7[Magma- 1300 K \\nLava- 1300 K \\nUranium- 2000 K]&f"]
	quest.0F14270F0A718C01.title: "&c发热物品&7[Warm Items]&f"
	quest.13471E64CDE49D27.quest_desc: [
		"&a&l精炼厂&r 会接收 2 种 &b流体&r,将它们混合并精炼成 1 种更好的 &b流体&r!\\n\\n这 2 种 &b流体&r 可以从端口以及左侧和右侧 &9输入&r.流体输出将从前方端口流出.\\n\\n你也可以使用 &b桶&r 将 &b流体&r 存入储罐!别忘了 &a右击&f &a&l精炼厂&r 来打开它的 GUI.我们需要在那里放入催化剂,才能启动机器.\\n除了催化剂,它还需要 &c能量&r,可以通过背面的端口添加!\\n&7[The lRefinery will take 2 Fluids and combine and refine them into 1 better Fluid! \\n\\nThe 2 Fluids can be Input from the Ports and the Left and Right sides. The Fluid Output will come out the Front Port. \\n\\nYou can use Buckets to deposit Fluids into the Tanks as well! Don't forget to Right Click the lRefinery to open its GUI. There we will need to place in a Catalyst, in order to start the Machine. \\nAlong with a Catalyst, it'll need Energy which can be added via the Port in the Back!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"首先,放置一排 5 个 &b&a流体管道&f&r.在中间,一侧放置 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r,另一侧放置 &7&a重型工程块&f&r.在剩余的 &b&a流体管道&f&r 旁边放置 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r.\\n&7[To start make a line of 5 Fluid Pipes. In the middle place Light Engineering Block on one side, and a Heavy Engineering Block on the other. Next to the rest of the Fluid Pipes place Steel Scaffolding.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_refinery1.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"在之前的工程块上放置更多工程块.在 &7&a重型工程块&f&r 的右侧,跳过 1 格,放置一个 &4&a红石工程块&f&r.在 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 旁边放置 2 个 2x2 的 &7&a铁板&f&r.\\n&7[Place more Engineering Blocks on the previous ones. To the right of the Heavy Engineering Block, skip 1 Block and place a Redstone Engineering Block. Next to the Light Engineering Block place 2 2x2 of Iron Sheetmetal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_refinery2.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"现在只需要再放几个 &7&a铁板&f&r!\\n&7[Now just a few more Iron Sheetmetals!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_refinery3.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"对于这个,我们需要用 &6工程师锤&f &a右击&f 顶部的 &7&a重型工程块&f&r.\\n&7[For this one we'll need to Right Click the top Heavy Engineering Block with our Hammer.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_refinery.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.13471E64CDE49D27.title: "&l&a精炼厂&7[lRefinery]&f"
	quest.135A16EDEEE27FA9.quest_desc: ["&8&l沉浸工程&r 中所有与 &c线缆&r 和 &c电力&r 相关的东西都可以分级.&6&a低压&f&r (&6LV&r)、&e&a中压&f&r (&eMV&r) 和 &5&a高压&f&r (&5HV&r).\\n\\n电压越高,可以传输和使用的 &c能量&r 就越多.有些机器需要更高的电压才能使用.\\n\\n为了传输不同的电压,你需要 &c变压器&r,去看看它们的任务吧!\\n&7[Everything related to Wires and power in lIE can be Tiered. Low Voltage (LV), Medium Voltage (MV), and High Voltage (HV). \\n\\nThe higher the Voltage the more Energy can be moved and used. Some Machines will need higher Voltage to be used. \\n\\nIn order to transfer different Voltages you'll need Transformers, check out their Quest!]&f"]
	quest.135A16EDEEE27FA9.title: "分级电压&7[Tiered Voltage]&f"
	quest.13AF35A3108B02AF.quest_desc: ["&a得以更快&f!\\n&7[Gotta go fast!]&f"]
	quest.1759A4E2AF0D2C88.quest_desc: ["想象一下 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r,现在只是让它的所有组件都更难制作!\\n\\n首先我们需要 &e琥珀金&r,这是一种由 &e金&r 和 &7银&r 在 &6&l&a合金窑&f&r 中制成的合金.\\n\\n其次我们需要 4 个 &8&a钢板金属块&f&r,就像 &7&a铁板&f&r 一样,需要 4 个 &8钢板&r 组合在一起.\\n\\n第三是我们的 &8&a钢质机械零件&f&r,它可以在工作台中用 1 个 &6&a铜锭&f&r 和 4 个 &8&a钢板&f&r 合成,或者在 &6工程师装配台&r 中更便宜地制作.\\n&7[Think of the Light Engineering Block, now just make all its components much harder to make! \\n\\n1st we need Electrum, which is an Alloy of Gold and Silver made in the lAlloy Kiln. \\n\\n2nd we need 4 Steel Sheetmetal, which like the Iron Sheetmetal, needs 4 Plates combined together. \\n\\n3rd is our Steel Mechanical Components which are either one Copper Ingot and 4 Steel Plates in a Crafting Table. or made cheaper in the Engineer's Workbench.]&f"]
	quest.1759A4E2AF0D2C88.title: "&7&a重型工程块&f&7[Heavy Engineering Block]&f"
	quest.18A9392BBCF5A871.quest_desc: ["和每个机器模组一样,&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r 需要一种方式来移动 &e物品&r、&b流体&r 等等!\\n\\n大多数机器都有默认设置的 &6输出&r 和 &9输入&r,但这些是可以配置的,比如使用 &6工程师螺丝刀&r!你可能还需要使用 &6工程师锤&f&r,但那是另一回事.\\n&7[Like every Machine Mod, lImmersive Engineering needs a way of moving Items, Fluids, and more! \\n\\nMost Machines will have default set Outputs and Inputs but these can be configured, like with the Engineer's Screwdriver! You also might need to use an Engineer's Hammer but that's different.]&f"]
	quest.18A9392BBCF5A871.title: "&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r 物流&7[lImmersive Engineering Logistics]&f"
	quest.1A13039D6302ADA5.quest_desc: ["你可以查看之前的任务来学习如何制作其中一些:&e&a轻型工程块&f&r 中的 &7&a铁质机械零件&f&r 和 &7&a重型工程块&f&r 中的 &8&a钢板金属块&f&r.\\n不过 &e琥珀金线圈&r 会有点不同……\\n\\n&e琥珀金线圈&r 需要 1 个 &a铁锭&f 和 8 个 MV 线缆线圈.要获得 MV 线缆线圈,我们需要用工程师剪线钳剪一些 &e琥珀金&r.\\n&7[You can check previous Quests to learn how to build some of these: Iron Mechanical Components in the Light Engineering Blocks and Steel Sheetmetal in Heavy Engineering Blocks. \\nThe Electrum Coils will be a bit different though... \\n\\nElectrum Coils need an Iron Ingot and 8 MV Wire Coils. To get MV Wire Coils we'll need to cut up some Electrum with Engineer's Wire Cutters.]&f"]
	quest.1A13039D6302ADA5.title: "&6&a发电机模块&f&7[Generator Block]&f"
	quest.1A3F053E0F693002.quest_desc: ["高级润滑系统将像耐久附魔一样作用于我们的 &8&a钻头&f&r 和 &8电锯锯片&r.\\n\\n它们在使用时会损失更少的耐久度.\\n&7[The Advanced Lubrication System will act like Unbreaking to our Drill Heads and Buzzsaw Blades. \\n\\nThey will lose less Durability on use.]&f"]
	quest.1A3F053E0F693002.quest_subtitle: "别笑它的名字!&7[Stop laughing at its name!]&f"
	quest.1A6A383B4EF26B20.quest_desc: ["&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r 没有太多选择,我们有 &7&a铁质钻体头部&f&r 或 &8&a钢质钻头&f&r.\\n\\n&7&a铁质钻体头部&f&r 以 &7&a铁镐&f&r 的等级挖掘 2x2 区域.它还能造成 6 点 &a伤害&f,并且耐久度比……\\n\\n&8&a钢质钻头&f&r 以 &b&a钻石镐&f&r 的相同等级挖掘 3x3 区域.这些能造成 7 点 &a伤害&f,并且有更高的耐久度!\\n&7[The lMining Drill doesn't have many choices, we have an Iron Drill Head or a Steel Drill Head. \\n\\nIron Drill Heads Mine in a 2x2 Area at the Tier of an Iron Pickaxe. It also does 6 Damage and has less Durability than the... \\n\\nSteel Drill Heads Mine in a 3x3 Area at the same Tier of a Diamond Pickaxe. These do 7 Damage and have more Durability!]&f"]
	quest.1A6A383B4EF26B20.title: "&8&a钻头&f&7[Drill Heads]&f"
	quest.1A8F2408970BFCCF.quest_desc: ["&e琥珀金&r 是一种由 &e金&r 和 &7银&r 制成的合金.\\n\\n从它的名字你可以猜到,它在所有与电力相关的东西中都有大量使用.线缆、连接器、变压器等等!\\n&7[Electrum is an Alloy made from Gold and Silver. \\n\\nYou can guess by its name it is used a ton in everything electricity related. Wires, Connectors, Transformers, ETC!]&f"]
	quest.1A8F2408970BFCCF.title: "&e&a琥珀金锭&f&r&7[Electrum Ingot]&f"
	quest.1BF02D43986ABB03.quest_desc: ["&e传送带&r 有各种不同的形状、尺寸和用途!\\n\\n首先,所有 &e&a传送带&f&r 都可以用 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 合成来给它们加上盖子.&e带盖传送带&r 会使 &e物品&r 在其上时无法被玩家拾取.\\n\\n&e传送带&r 的第一个也是最简单的版本是 &e垂直传送带&r.它只是将 &e物品&r 向上运送!\\n\\n&e分流传送带&r……会分流 &e物品&r 前进的方向.它会为每个 &e物品&r 切换:1 个向左,1 个向右,1 个向左,1 个向右.\\n\\n&e掉落传送带&r 会将 &e物品&r 掉落到其下方的容器中,或者如果有开放空间,就只是掉落 &e物品&r.这些可以用 &4红石&r 配置为不掉落 &e物品&r.\\n\\n最后是 &e提取传送带&r,这个会自动从容器中取出 &e物品&r 并将其部署在其 &e传送带&r 上.这些也可以与一些机器一起使用!\\n&7[Belts come in all different shapes and sizes and uses! \\n\\nFirst, all Conveyor Belts can be Crafted with Steel Scaffolding to give them covers. Covered Belts will make it so Items can't be picked up from Players while on it. \\n\\nThe first and simplest version of the Belt is the Vertical Belt. It simply takes Items upwards! \\n\\nSplitting Belts... split the directions the Items going in, go. It will switch for every Item: 1 goes Left, 1 goes Right, 1 goes Left, 1 goes Right. \\n\\nDropping Belts will drop the Items either into an Inventory below it, or if there is open space it will just drop the Items. These can be configured with Redstone to not drop Items. \\n\\nThe last is the Extracting Belt, this one will automatically take Items out from Inventories and deploy it on its Belt. These can also be used with some Machines!]&f"]
	quest.1BF02D43986ABB03.title: "&e传送带&r 的类型&7[Types of Belts]&f"
	quest.1C76E244AE3582E6.quest_desc: [
		"&5&l装配器&r 与大多数机器不同,主要在其 GUI 中工作.\\n\\n&a右击&f 机器,通过将配方放入屏幕顶部的网格中来设置 3 个配方.它们排列的顺序,就是它遵循的优先级顺序.\\n\\n你可以从 &e传送带&r &9输入 &e物品&r,它们会从后面的 &a传送带&r &6输出&r.你还可以 &6输入 &b流体&r,这些流体会用于补充合成中使用的 &b桶&r 或 &b储罐&r!\\n\\n你还需要从顶部用 &c能量&r 为其供电.\\n&7[The lAssembler, unlike most Machines, work mostly in its GUI. \\n\\nRight Click the Machine and set up 3 Recipes, by putting them into the Grids at the top of the screen. The order they are in, is the order it will follow for priority. \\n\\nYou can Input Items from the Belts and they will Output out of the back Belts. You can also Input Fluids which will be used to refill Buckets or Tanks used in Crafting! \\n\\nYou'll also need to power it with Energy from the Top.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"放置 2 条平行的、各由 3 个 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 组成的线,中间留 &a1 格&f 空间.在它们之间,中心放置一个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r,周围放置 &4&a红石工程块&f&r.\\n&7[Place 2 parallel lines of 3 Steel Scaffolding with a Block of space in between them. Between them place a Light Engineering Block in the center, and Redstone Engineering Blocks around it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_assembler1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"在有 &4&a红石工程块&f&r 的侧面放置 &7&a铁板&f&r.然后,在 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 上方,我们当然需要另一个.之后,放置 &e&a传送带&f&r,通向并穿过 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r!\\n&7[On the sides with Redstone Engineering Blocks place Iron Sheetmetal. Then, above the Light Engineering Block we of course will need another. After, place Conveyor Belts going to and through the Light Engineering Block!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_assemble2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"这个单看可能有点令人困惑；在我们之前放置的 &7&a铁板&f&r 上放置 &7&a铁板台阶&f&r.然后,在它们之间放置完整的 &7&a铁板&f&r.\\n&7[This one might be confusing just be sight alone; place Iron Sheetmetal Slabs on our previously placed Iron Sheetmetal. Then, between them place full Iron Sheetmetal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_assembler3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"要建造我们的 &5&l装配器&r,用我们可爱的 &6工程师锤&f &a右击&f 第一个 &e&a传送带&f&r!\\n&7[To build our lAssembler Right Click the first Conveyor Belt with our lovely Hammer!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_assembler.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1C76E244AE3582E6.title: "&5&l装配器&7[lAssembler]&f"
	quest.1D4E7F548431263A.quest_desc: ["这无疑是这些方块中最容易制作的.\\n\\n铁和 &4红石&r 你只需通过 &2&l原版&r 游戏获得,唯一”困难”的物品是 &7&a铁板&f&r.\\n&7[Easily the simplest of these Blocks to make. \\n\\nIron and Redstone you'll just get from lVanilla gameplay, the only \"difficult\" Item is the Iron Sheetmetal.]&f"]
	quest.1D4E7F548431263A.title: "&4&a红石工程块&f&7[Redstone Engineering Block]&f"
	quest.1F7DA060792D716A.quest_desc: [
		"&d&l搅拌机&r 就像你的母亲/祖母用来将鸡蛋与面粉和糖混合,以烘焙她们正在制作的美味点心的那种机器!\\n\\n&d&l搅拌机&r 会混合 &e物品&r 和 &b流体&r.要输入 &b流体&r,我们需要使用 &d&l搅拌机&r 左侧的端口.要给它 &e物品&r,我们需要使用背面的端口.\\n\\n为了工作,它需要从 &d&l搅拌机&r 正面顶部的端口输入 &c能量&r.\\n\\n一旦混合完成,我们的结果将从机器正面的端口出来!\\n&7[The lMixer is just like the ones your Mother/Grandmother uses to mix eggs into flour and sugar to bake whatever delicious treat they are making! \\n\\nThe lMixer will mix Items and Fluids. To get Fluids in we'll need to use the Port on the Left Side of the lMixer. To give it Items we'll need to use the Ports at the back. \\n\\nIn order to work it'll need Energy put into it from the Port at the Top of the Front of the lMixer. \\n\\nOnce it mixes, our result will come out the Port in the Front of the Machine!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&d&l搅拌机&r 的第一层建得像一个 Wi-Fi 符号!首先是 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r,然后是 &b&a流体管道&f&r,以及 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r.\\n&7[The first layer of the lMixer is built like a Wifi Symbol! First is Light Engineering Block, then Fluid Pipes, and Steel Scaffolding.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_mixer1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"在我们的 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 上方,我们会再放一个,并在新放置的那个 &a左侧&f 再放一个.在最右边的 &8钢脚手架&f&r 上,我们会放置一个 &4&a红石工程块&f&r.然后,我们会在机器的背面放置一个 2x2 的 &7&a铁板&f&r.\\n&7[Above our Light Engineering Block we'll put another and one to the left of the newly placed one. On the far right Scaffolding we'll place a Redstone Engineering Block. Then, we'll place a 2x2 of Iron Sheetmetal on the back of our Machine.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_mixer2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"在第三个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 顶部,我们会放置一个单独的 &8&a钢栅栏&f&r,它的 &a右侧&f 将是第四个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r.\\n&7[On top of the third Light Engineering Block we'll place a singular Steel Fence, and to the right of it will be a fourth Light Engineering Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_mixer3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"要创建 &d&l搅拌机&r,用 &6工程师锤&f &a右击&f 我们 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 和 &4&a红石工程块&f&r 之间的 &7&a铁板&f&r!\\n&7[To create the lMixer Right Click the Iron Sheetmetal between our Light Engineering Block and Redstone Engineering Block with a Engineer's Hammer!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_mixer.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1F7DA060792D716A.title: "&l&d搅拌机&7[lMixer]&f"
	quest.1FA44E8FEE004AB4.quest_desc: ["&a麻绳&f 和 &8&a钢缆&f&r 可以像普通 &c线缆&r 一样放置在 &c连接器&r 和 &c继电器&r 上,但不会传输 &c能量&r.\\n\\n相反,它们用于装饰或使用 &6&l工程师天钩&r!\\n&7[Hemp Rope and Steel Cables are placed like normal Wires on Connectors and Relays but won't transfer Energy. \\n\\nInstead they are for Decor or using the lEngineer's Skyhook!]&f"]
	quest.1FA44E8FEE004AB4.title: "&6&l天钩&r 使用安全!&7[Safe for lSkyhook usage!]&f"
	quest.2224AA108FC006F3.quest_desc: ["&a左轮快速装弹器&f 实际上不是一个升级,而是一个单独的物品,用于提供帮助.\\n\\n像 &d&l左轮手枪&r 一样给它装满弹夹,但现在每当你需要为 &d&l左轮手枪&r 重新装弹时,你只需用它 &a右击&f 即可瞬间装弹!\\n&7[The Revolver Speedloader isn't actually an Upgrade, rather it is a separate Item that's used to help. \\n\\nFill it with Cartridges like the lRevolver, but now whenever you need to Reload the lRevolver you can just Right Click with it to instantly reload!]&f"]
	quest.2224AA108FC006F3.quest_subtitle: "我开了 6 枪？还是只开了 5 枪？&7[Did I shoot 6 times? Or only 5?]&f"
	quest.2262AB9F934165D0.quest_desc: ["我不在乎你怎么得到它,我只需要你得到它!\\n\\n&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r 为 &8钢&r 添加了比简单建造多得多的用途,几乎所有的东西都需要 &8钢&r 来制作!\\n\\n主要是工具、&a机械零件&f 和建筑方块.很多都是用 &8&a钢板&f&r 或 &8钢脚手架&f&r 制作的.\\n\\n你会需要很多,但 &l&c&a粗制高炉&f&r 和 &l&6合金窑&r 无法自动化,所以我们可能需要一个……\\n&7[I don't care how you got it, I just need you to get it! \\n\\nlImmersive Engineering adds a whole lot more uses to Steel than just simple builds, almost everything will need Steel to make it! \\n\\nTools, Mechanical Parts, and Building Blocks mainly. A lot are made with Steel Plates or Scaffolding. \\n\\nYou'll need a lot of it but the lCrude Blast Furnace and lAlloy Kin can't be automated so we might need a... ]&f"]
	quest.2262AB9F934165D0.title: "&8&a钢锭&f&7[Steel Ingot]&f"
	quest.231E0C0A9B0C0509.quest_desc: ["这个可以连接到你的 &c&l&a蓄电池背包&f&r 上.\\n\\n当穿戴 &c&l背包&r 时,附近的 &e物品&r 会被吸入你的物品栏!\\n&7[This one can attach to your lAccumulator Backpack. \\n\\nWhen the lBackpack is worn, Items nearby will be sucked into your Inventory!]&f"]
	quest.23FDFA44A162023A.quest_desc: ["&6工程师装配台&r 是许多合成和升级所需的必要方块.\\n\\n我们可以将其与 &9蓝图&r 一起使用,来合成我们在其他地方无法合成的特殊物品.将 &9蓝图&r 放入左侧槽位,将我们的 &e合成材料&r 放入右侧槽位.\\n\\n或者我们可以把工具扔进去,为它们添加升级,比如左轮手枪或 &a采矿钻头&f!\\n\\n另外,当你添加 &e物品&r 和 &9蓝图&r 时,你可以在 &6方块&r 本身上看到它们,非常酷!\\n&7[The Engineer's Workbench is a necessary Block needed for many Crafts and Upgrades. \\n\\nWe can use it with Blueprints to Craft special Items that we can't Craft elsewhere. Put the Blueprints in the Left Slot, and our Crafting Items into the Right Slots.\\n\\nOr we can throw our Tools into it, to add Upgrades to them, like the Revolver or Mining Drill! \\n\\nAlso when you add Items and Blueprints you can see them on the Block itself, pretty cool!]&f"]
	quest.23FDFA44A162023A.title: "&6工程师装配台&7[Engineer's Workbench]&f"
	quest.251464B43353D4C6.quest_desc: ["我们心爱的&a园艺玻璃罩&f!它是一个自动化农场,通过这个任务,使用起来很简单!\\n\\n首先,它需要从左侧、右侧或顶部输入&c能量&6输入&r!\\n\\n然后,它需要从后端口输入&9水&r(可以尝试使用&9水槽&r).\\n\\n接下来,我们需要通过底部的&e物品&6输入&r输入种子、耕地和可选的肥料!\\n\\n它需要与种子匹配的正确耕地,顺便说一下,你可以通过&a右击&f玻璃罩查看其GUI来检查所有这些!\\n\\n一旦它拥有了所有这些东西,它就会快速生长并收获你的作物,并在罩子的前部&6输出&r它们.\\n\\n最后注意:它会保留原始种子和耕地,不会消耗它们,泥土会被制成耕地,肥料包括硫磺、矿渣、硝酸盐和&a工业肥料&f.\\n&7[Our beloved Garden Cloche! It is an automatic Farm, and with this Quest is simple to use! \\n\\nTo start it will need Energy Input from either the Left, Right, or Top! \\n\\nIt will then need Water from Back Port, (try using a Sink). \\n\\nNext, we'll need to Input our Seeds, Farmland, and optional Fertilizer by the Item Input at the Bottom! \\n\\nIt will need the correct Farmland for the Seeds, you can check this all by Right Clicking the Cloche to see its GUI BTW! \\n\\nOnce it has all that, it will quickly grow and harvest your Crops and Output them on the Front of the Dome. \\n\\nLast notes: it will keep the original Seed and Farmland and won't use them up, Dirt will be made into Farmland, and the Fertilizers are Sulfur, Slag, Nitrate, and Industrial Fertilizer.]&f"]
	quest.252A24CED69C1882.quest_desc: ["&a热力发电机&f,我打算简称它为热力机,是一种独特的发电机.\\n\\n它本身不会做任何事情,我们需要做的是在热力机的不同侧面放置不同温度的方块或流体.\\n\\n温差越大,它产生的能量就越多!\\n&7[The Thermoelectric Generator, which I am going to just be calling a Thermo, is a unique Generator. \\n\\nOn its own it won't do anything, what we'll need to do is place Blocks or Fluids of differenting Temperatures on different sides of the Thermo. \\n\\nThe bigger the difference in Temperature the more Energy it creates!]&f"]
	quest.252A24CED69C1882.title: "来自温度的能量&7[Energy from Temperature]&f"
	quest.257C80468B080B3C.quest_desc: ["&a电磁铁&f是&8&lIE&r对&a吸收漏斗&f的诠释.\\n\\n嗯,差不多吧!它不会储存&e物品&r,而是会将它们移动到最靠近电磁铁顶面的位置.\\n\\n这可以用来将它们放到&e传送带&r或漏斗上!\\n\\n不过,它需要消耗&c能量&r才能使用.\\n&7[The Electromagnet is lIE's take on the Absorption Hopper. \\n\\nWell, kinda! It won't hold the Items rather they will be moved closest to the Top face of the Electromagnet. \\n\\nThis can be used to get them onto Belts or hoppers! \\n\\nIt will require Energy to be used though.]&f"]
	quest.27FA2DB7839172BB.quest_desc: ["默认情况下,&c&l背包&r只会为你手中的&e物品&r和你穿戴的盔甲充电.但如果我们想给更多东西充电呢!\\n\\n那么我们就需要&a感应充电器&f!装上这个后,你物品栏中所有可以充电的&e物品&r都会充电.\\n&7[The lBackpack by default will only charge Items in your Hand and Armor you are wearing. But what if we wanted to charge more than that! \\n\\nThen we'll need the Induction Charger! With this attached, every Item in your Inventory that can take charge, will charge.]&f"]
	quest.288406DE6DA31BA6.quest_desc: ["很多东西都需要&c能量&r,尤其是在&8&lIE&r中.要开始,我们需要一些&6工程师的钢丝钳&r!\\n\\n你可以用它们把一些板材剪成&c导线&r,然后放入&c线圈&r中,以备使用.\\n\\n它们也用于从&c连接器&r上取下&c导线&r.\\n&7[Lots of things need Energy, especially in lIE. To get started we'll need some Engineer's Wire Cutters! \\n\\nYou can use those to snip some Plates into Wires which can then be put into Coils, ready for use. \\n\\nThey are also used for taking Wires off Connectors.]&f"]
	quest.288406DE6DA31BA6.title: "&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r 之力!&7[lImmersive Engineering Power!]&f"
	quest.28847A536C38EEA0.quest_desc: ["&c变压器&r是我们从&6低压&r连接升级到&e中压&r连接的方式.小的&c连接器&r是&6低压&r,大的那个是&e中压&r!\\n\\n如果你想从&e中压&r升级到&5高压&r,我们需要一个&5&a高压变压器&f&r.这些和另一个&c变压器&r工作原理相同,只是小的&c连接器&r是&e中压&r,大的那个是&5高压&r!\\n\\n不,没有&e中压&r,你不能直接从&6低压&r升级到&5高压&r!\\n&7[Transformers are how we go from LV Connections to MV Connections. The little Connector is LV and bigger one is MV! \\n\\nIf you want to go from MV to HV we'll need an HV Transformer. These work the same as the other Transformer, just the smaller Connector is MV and bigger one is HV! \\n\\nNo, you can't go from LV to HV without MV!]&f"]
	quest.28847A536C38EEA0.quest_subtitle: "迈克尔·贝执导&7[Directed by Michael Bay]&f"
	quest.28847A536C38EEA0.title: "&c变压器&7[Transformers]&f"
	quest.28E99A6E17E86709.quest_desc: ["输送&b流体&r是&8&l沉浸工程&r的重要组成部分,想想&a杂酚油&f和&a植物燃油&f!\\n\\n&b&a流体管道&f&r是我们输送&b流体&r的基本方式,如果你想让它们更快,可以看看&b&a液泵&f&r.\\n\\n&b&a流体管道&f&r,和能量连接器一样,根据它们连接到什么来决定&9输入&r和&6输出&r.有些机器需要&4&a红石信号&f&r才能向&b&a流体管道&f&r&6输出&r,比如&b&l储罐&r!\\n\\n我们可以用&6工程师锤&r来改变&b管道&r的连接对象,另外我们可以在它们上面使用&8&a钢脚手架&f&r来覆盖它们,或者用染料给它们染色!\\n&7[Moving Fluids is an essential part of lIE, just think of the Creosote Oil and Plant Oil! \\n\\nFluid Pipes are our basic ways of moving Fluids, if you want them faster check out Fluid Pumps. \\n\\nFluid Pipes, like Energy Connectors, are determined where to Input and Output from what they are connected to. Some Machines need Redstone Signals to Output to Fluid Pipes, like the lTank! \\n\\nWe can use an Engineer's Hammer to change what the Pipes connect to, plus we can use Steel Scaffolding on them to cover them, or Dye to dye them!]&f"]
	quest.28E99A6E17E86709.title: "输送&b流体&7[Moving Fluids]&f"
	quest.29C9F8719DA63D8D.quest_desc: ["&2&l链锯&r的工作原理类似于&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r,只是针对&2树木&r!\\n\\n它需要&2生物柴油&r作为燃料,这里我也不解释怎么获得!\\n\\n还需要某种&8锯片&r.你可以通过&6工程师装配台&r的顶部槽位安装.\\n\\n只需砍断&2树&r上的原木,每块原木、树叶和鸟巢都会随之掉落!你可以按住潜行键来避免砍断所有相连的部分.\\n\\n&2&l链锯&r也能造成10点&a伤害&f!天哪,为什么还要用剑？哦对了,&8锯&r有耐久度而且需要&2生物柴油&r.\\n\\n&2&l链锯&r可以容纳1个&8锯片&r或&8圆锯片&r以及2个升级.\\n&7[The lBuzzsaw works similar to the lMining Drill, just for Trees! \\n\\nIt requires Bio-Diesel as Fuel, which I won't explain how to get here either! \\n\\nAnd some sort of Sawblade. Which you can attach via the Top Slot in the Engineer's Workbench. \\n\\nSimply break Logs on a Tree and every Log, Leaf, and Birds Nest will come down with it! You can hold Shift to not break everything attached. \\n\\nThe lBuzzsaw also does 10 Damage! Dang, why even use a Sword? Oh yeah Saws have Durability and it needs Bio-Diesel. \\n\\nThe lBuzzsaw can hold 1 Blade or Disk and 2 Upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.29C9F8719DA63D8D.title: "&2&l链锯&7[lBuzzsaw]&f"
	quest.2A1BFB2E0F1F3312.quest_desc: ["&d&a末地烛&f&r也能造成10点&a伤害&f,并且能击中末影人.\\n&5末影珍珠&r不会击中生物,而是会在发射时将你传送得更远.\\n&3三叉戟&r像正常的&3三叉戟&r投掷一样,造成8点&a伤害&f.\\n&c&a烈焰棒&f&r造成10点&a伤害&f并使生物着火!\\n&7[End Rod does 10 Damage as well as hits Endermen. \\nEnderpearls won't hit Mobs, rather they will teleport you much farther when shot. \\nTrident acts like a normal Trident throw, dealing 8 Damage. \\nBlaze Rods deal 10 Damage and set the Mobs on Fire!]&f"]
	quest.2A1BFB2E0F1F3312.title: "来自&2&lMinecraft&r的&5&l磁轨炮&r弹药&7[lRailgun Ammo from lMinecraft]&f"
	quest.2E89A03BA809634E.quest_desc: ["这些只能与军械师交易获得.\\n\\n&a特种子弹&f是那些有独特效果的子弹!\\n\\n追踪弹、爆炸弹和信号弹需要用这些&9蓝图&r来合成.\\n&7[These can only be Traded with Gunsmiths for. \\n\\nSpecialized Projectiles are ones that do unique things! \\n\\nHoming, Explosive, and Flares are needed to be Crafted with these Blueprints.]&f"]
	quest.2E89A03BA809634E.title: "&9&a特种子弹&f蓝图&7[Specialized Projectiles Blueprints ]&f"
	quest.2E9D1131DC21CC5B.quest_desc: ["&l&d工业先锋&f&r有其时尚的未来主义设计,&5&l&d通用机械&f&r有其朴素的现代设计,而&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r则更加复古!\\n\\n一切都是&6棕色&r、&7灰色&r和&8&a深灰色&f&r!\\n\\n这个模组都始于&6工程师锤&r.这些可以用来制作板材、粉末,或者只是建造我们的多方块结构!\\n\\n顺便问一下,我告诉过你我们会在这个模组里做很多那些东西吗？希望你喜欢它们!\\n&7[lIndustrial Foregoing has its sleak futuristic design, lMekanism has its dull modern design, and lImmersive Engineering takes it much more retro! \\n\\nEverything is Brown, Grey, and Dark Grey! \\n\\nThe Mod all starts with the Engineer's Hammer. These can be used to make Plates, Dust, or just building our Multiblocks! \\n\\nBTW, did I tell you we'll be making a lot of those in this Mod? Hope you like them!]&f"]
	quest.2E9D1131DC21CC5B.title: "&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&7[lImmersive Engineering]&f"
	quest.2F19529214CA9559.quest_desc: ["它就像荆棘附魔,但不会造成&a伤害&f,只会让攻击者迷失方向.\\n\\n它只会让生物停下一小会儿,对玩家来说更有效(也更烦人)!\\n&7[It's like Thorns but doesn't Damage, just disorients Attackers. \\n\\nIt'll just stop Mobs for a little, it is much more effective (and aggravating) to Players!]&f"]
	quest.2F19529214CA9559.quest_subtitle: "闪电？&7[Blitz?]&f"
	quest.2F8D117F802FEAF0.quest_desc: ["突击队员是轻装部队.\\n\\n他们有12颗心,没有护甲.\\n\\n他们的武器是一把&d&l左轮手枪&r和一个他们拿在副手上的盾牌.\\n\\n死亡时,他们会掉落具有不同属性的左轮手枪零件,类似于&d神化&f的属性!\\n&7[Commandos are the light troops. \\n\\nThey have 12 Hearts and no Armor. \\n\\nTheir weapon is a lRevolver and a Shield they hold in their Offhand. \\n\\nOn death they will drop Revolver parts with different stats, similar to Apotheosis stats!]&f"]
	quest.2F8D117F802FEAF0.title: "突击队员&7[Commando]&f"
	quest.30EA16BB8C169F86.quest_desc: ["这是&6铜&r和&7锡&r的合金!\\n\\n它在&7&l&d现代工业化&f&r中被大量使用!但在&8&l沉浸工程&r中……用得不多……\\n&7[This one is a combination of Copper and Tin! \\n\\nIt's used a ton in lModern Industrialization! But in lIE... not that much...]&f"]
	quest.30EA16BB8C169F86.title: "&6&a青铜锭&f&7[Bronze Ingot]&f"
	quest.31324A6F96CAC112.quest_desc: ["&b&a液泵&f&r不仅用于装瓶机,它们还可以用来更快地输送&b流体&r……!\\n\\n使用&6工程师锤&r,我们可以将&b&a液泵&f&r的侧面设置为&9输入&r和&6输出&r.\\n\\n然后,我们可以用&4红石&r或&c能量&r为其供能,使用&c能量&r输送&b流体&r比&4红石&r快得多.\\n&7[Fluid Pumps aren't just used for Bottlers, they can also be used to move Fluids... quicker! \\n\\nUsing an Engineer's Hammer we can set Sides of the Fluid Pump to Inputs and Outputs. \\n\\nThen, we can Power it with Redstone or Energy, with Energy moving Fluids much faster than Redstone.]&f"]
	quest.31324A6F96CAC112.title: "&b&a液泵&f&7[Fluid Pump]&f"
	quest.320EE52EB022FAD3.quest_desc: ["这个很有趣!\\n\\n&b&a流体排出口&f&r可以设置为&9输入&b流体&r,然后我们可以让它将这些&b流体&r作为源方块放置在&6输出&r侧面的旁边!\\n\\n这意味着我们可以自动化放置&9水&r、&c熔岩&r或几乎任何&b流体&r!\\n&7[Now this is a fun one! \\n\\nFluid Outlets can be set to Input Fluids, and then we can have it so it places those Fluids as Source Blocks next to the Output Sides! \\n\\nThis means we can automate placing of Water, Lava, or pretty much any Fluids! ]&f"]
	quest.320EE52EB022FAD3.title: "&b&a流体排出口&f&7[Fluid Outlet]&f"
	quest.32384DE59539557D.quest_desc: [
		"&4&l粉碎机&r是一个非常危险且嘈杂的机器.\\n\\n你可以从顶部的格栅&9输入&e物品&r(或生物),它会将它们&4&l粉碎&r成它们的掉落物!\\n\\n这非常有用,特别是将&a粗矿&f粉碎成粉末.如果我们使用粗矿块,它会比&6锤子&r给出更多的粉末,而且有些还有机会给出一种全新的粉末类型!\\n\\n所有掉落物都会从底部前方的方块出来,自动&6弹出&r.它还需要从顶部&a右侧&f输入&c能量&r.\\n&7[The lCrusher is a very dangerous and loud Machine. \\n\\nYou can Input Items (or Mobs) into the Top Grates, and it will lCrush them into their Drops! \\n\\nThis can be very helpful especially with taking Raw Ores into Dust. If we use Raw Ore Blocks it will give us more Dust than what the Hammer will give, also some have a chance at giving an entirely new type of Dust! \\n\\nAll the Drops will come out of the Bottom Front Block, automatically ejecting. It will also need Energy Input from the Top Right Side.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&4&l粉碎机&r相当大,我们需要放置这个由&8&a钢脚手架&f&r和&e&a轻型工程块&f&r组成的布局.&e&a轻型工程块&f&r朝向的那一面是正面!\\n&7[The lCrusher is pretty big, we'll need to place this layout of Steel Scaffolding and Light Engineering Blocks. The direction the Light Engineering Blocks face is the Front side!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crusher1.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
		"在我们已有的3个&e&a轻型工程块&f&r上面,我们再放置3个.我们还会在左侧放置一个&4&a红石工程块&f&r和&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.然后,在中间再放一个&e&a泛光灯&f&r,并用&8&a钢栅栏&f&r围起来.\\n&7[On top of our 3 Light Engineering Blocks we'll place 3 more. We'll also place a Redstone Engineering Block and Light Engineering Block on the Left Side. Then, put another Light Block in the middle and surround it with Steel Fences.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crusher2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后,我们只需在&8&a钢栅栏&f&r上面和中间扔9个漏斗!\\n&7[Finally, we just throw 9 Hoppers on top of the Steel Fences and in the middle!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crusher3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"你需要敲击中间的&8栅栏&r来形成多方块结构.\\n&7[You'll need to smack the middle Fence to make the Multiblock.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_crusher.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.32384DE59539557D.title: "&l&4粉碎机&7[lCrusher]&f"
	quest.33732EE8110A0911.quest_desc: ["&8&l沉浸工程&r的开发者忘了&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r也可以用于采矿,所以最后一刻他加入了时运III.\\n\\n那就是&a岩石软化酸&f.\\n&7[The lIE Dev forgot the lMining Drill can also be used for Mining so last minute he put in Fortune III. \\n\\nThat being the Rock Softening Acid.]&f"]
	quest.340F93695FFF8D76.quest_desc: ["With this the lChemical Thrower will be more of a Chemical Shooter. \\n\\nThe range will be increased but the spray width will be decreased. So it is more accurate!"]
	quest.341BB1353A1E45EA.quest_desc: ["&a机枪炮塔&f将像一个带有电脑大脑的&d&l左轮手枪&r一样工作!\\n\\n它们需要从下方输入&c能量&r,以及一个&4&a红石信号&f&r来开启.或者用&6工程师螺丝刀&f&r点击它使其始终保持开启.\\n\\n它使用与&d&l左轮手枪&r相同的弹药,包括特种弹头!你可以向它&9输入&r子弹并&6输出&r弹壳,或者通过弹出弹壳按钮让弹壳掉落.\\n\\n在开始射击之前,我们需要设置它的目标.首先,它不会攻击放置它的人.我们还有一个类型栏,可以添加任何玩家或生物名称来加入.这些设置会使它放过它们!\\n\\n它默认设置为黑名单,如果是黑名单模式,意味着它会射击列表中的目标.然后我们有”动物”选项,指的是&a被动型生物&f.”玩家”选项仅指玩家.”中立”选项代表任何中立生物和村民.别担心,它总是会以&a敌对性生物&f为目标!\\n&7[Gun Turrets will act as a lRevolver with a Computer brain! \\n\\nThey'll need Energy from below it, and a Redstone Signal to turn on. Or use an Engineer's Screwdriver on it to make it always on. \\n\\nIt uses the same Ammo as a lRevolver, that includes Speciality Projectiles! You can Input Bullets into it and Output the Casings, or just have them dropped out with the Expel Casing Button. \\n\\nBefore it starts shooting, we'll need to set its targeting. First, it won't attack the person who placed it. We also have a Type Bar we can add any Player or Mob name to Add in. These will make it so it spares them! \\n\\nIt is automatically set to Blacklist, if it is Blacklisted that means it'll Shoot what is listed. We then have Animals which means Passive Mobs. Players means just Players. Neutral stands for any Neutral Mobs and Villagers. Don't worry it was always target Hostile Mobs!]&f"]
	quest.34D09336FA3E272A.quest_desc: ["&a化学喷射炮塔&f具有与&a机枪炮塔&f完全相同的目标选择机制,所以去那里&a了解更多信息&f!\\n\\n就像&a机枪炮塔&f一样,&a化学喷射炮塔&f需要从其端口输入&c能量&r.但它还需要通过管道输入&b流体&r来储存和发射.使用管道&9输入&b流体&r,因为你不能用&b桶&f&r填充它,只能用&b管道&r.\\n\\n&a化学喷射炮塔&f的存储容量为4,000mB或4&b桶&f&r.你还可以按下一个按钮来点燃抛出的&b流体&r.这会使可燃&b流体&r着火!\\n&7[The Chemthrower Turret has the same exact targeting as the Gun Turret so check there for more info! \\n\\nJust like the Gun Turret, the Chemthrower Turret needs Energy from its ports. But it will also need Fluids Piped in to hold and shoot. Input Fluids with Pipes as you can't use Buckets to fill it, only Pipes. \\n\\nThe Chemthrower Turret has a storage of 4,000mB or 4 Buckets. You can also press a Button to Ignite Fluids that are thrown. This will set Flammable Fluids, on fire!]&f"]
	quest.35E399D88D2EDCB6.quest_desc: ["有了这个升级,每个攻击你的人都会:1. 被击晕,这会让他们停下一秒钟；2. 受到伤害；3. 摧毁任何抛射物.\\n\\n我认为这个升级是值得的!\\n&7[With this Upgrade everyone who attacks you will 1. be Stunned which will stop them for a second 2. hurt them and 3. destroy any Projectiles. \\n\\nI think it's worth the Upgrade!]&f"]
	quest.35E399D88D2EDCB6.quest_subtitle: "冲突？&7[Clash?]&f"
	quest.36EB83BB41A9E621.quest_desc: [
		"&b&l储罐&r就像&l&e筒仓&r,但是用于&b流体&r!\\n\\n它只能容纳一种类型的&b流体&r,但可以容纳51&a2桶&f那种&b流体&r.\\n\\n你可以从顶部或&a下面&f&9输入&b流体&r,但只能从底部&6输出&r.\\n&7[The lTank is just like the lSilo but for Fluids! \\n\\nIt can hold only 1 type of Fluid, but it can hold 512 Buckets of that Fluid. \\n\\nYou can Input Fluid from the Top or Bottom Side, but you can only Output from the Bottom.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&b&l储罐&r的建造方式类似于&e&l筒仓&r,从我们的防腐木栅栏和单个&7&a铁板&f金属&r开始.\\n&7[The lTank is built similar to the lSilo, start with our Treated Fences and singular Iron Sheetmetal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_tank1.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"现在我们在栅栏上方建造空心的&7&a铁板&f金属&r方块,这次是3格高.\\n&7[Now we build our hollow squares of Iron Sheetmetals above our Fences, this time 3 Blocks high.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_tank2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_tank3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_tank4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后,用填满的&7&a铁板&f金属&r方块封顶!\\n&7[Then, top it off with a filled in square of Iron Sheetmetal!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_tank5.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"&a右击&f与&e&l筒仓&r中相同的方块来创建我们的&b&l储罐&r.\\n&7[Right Click the same Block as in the lSilo to create our lTank.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_tank.png width:100 height:120 align:center}"
	]
	quest.36EB83BB41A9E621.title: "&b&l储罐&7[lTank]&f"
	quest.373668AE257A7A94.quest_desc: ["&a烈性炸药&f弹筒会向你的敌人发射爆炸物,像TNT一样炸毁附近的一切!\\n\\n龙息弹丸像霰弹一样工作,但现在抛射物着火了!!!!!\\n\\n&a药剂弹头&f根据其制作时使用的药水给予&a药水效果&f.\\n\\n&a信号弹&f像弩中的烟花一样工作.\\n\\n&a追踪弹&f会瞄准离你最近的任何生物……希望那是个危险的生物.\\n\\n狼群弹丸像霰弹弹丸,但现在抛射物是&a追踪弹&f!\\n&7[High Explosive Cartridges will shoot explosives at your Enemies, blowing up everything nearby like TNT would! \\n\\nDragon's Breath Shells work like Buckshot, but now the Projectiles are on Fire!!!!! \\n\\nPhial Cartridges give Potion Effects based on the Potion used in its creation. \\n\\nFlare Shells work like Fireworks in a Crossbow. \\n\\nHoming Cartridges will aim after whatever Mob is closest to you... let's hope it's a dangerous Mob. \\n\\nWolfpack Shells are like Buckshot Shells but now the Projectiles are Homing Cartridges!]&f"]
	quest.373668AE257A7A94.title: "&a特种子弹&f&7[Specialized Projectiles]&f"
	quest.38C98FCB6A2D4226.quest_desc: ["微型特斯拉线圈将像荆棘附魔一样工作.\\n\\n任何在你穿着&c&l背包&f&r时击中你的人,都会被电击.造成&a伤害&f并给予一个效果!\\n&7[The Miniature Telsa Coil will act like the Thorns Enchantment. \\n\\nAnyone who hits you, while you are wearing the lBackpack, will be Shocked. Dealing Damage and giving an Effect!]&f"]
	quest.38F01BAEC74D5D68.quest_desc: ["它和另一个预热器一样,我只是想让它们对称而已:D.\\n&7[It's the same as the other Preheater I just wanted it to be symmetrical :D.]&f"]
	quest.39DAC0592300992A.quest_desc: ["&9&a金属冲压模具&f蓝图&r可以合成.\\n\\n&7&l&a金属冲压机&f多方块结构&r将自动化&7&a金属板材&f&r和&e物品&r的制造.\\n\\n要冲压&7金属&r,我们需要模具.\\n\\n为了制作模具,我们需要这些&9蓝图&r!\\n&7[Metal Press Mold Blueprints can be Crafted. \\n\\nlMetal Press Multiblock will automate the creation of Metal Plates and Items. \\n\\nTo press the Metals we'll need Molds. \\n\\nIn order to make the Molds will need these Blueprints!]&f"]
	quest.39DAC0592300992A.title: "&9&a金属冲压模具&f蓝图&7[Metal Press Molds Blueprints ]&f"
	quest.3A4A8EAA3022C7BA.quest_desc: ["&a水车&f是我们可以用于&a动能发电机&f的机器之一.\\n\\n这些更加紧凑但也更昂贵,&a相比&f于风车.\\n\\n要使用它们,你需要让&9水&r流过水车.周围的&9水&r越多,它转得越快.只要确保&9水&r不是以两种不同的方式流动!\\n\\n更紧凑意味着我们可以在1个&a动能发电机&f上放置3个水车以获得更多能量.\\n&7[Water Wheels are one of the Machines we can use for the Kinetic Dynamo. \\n\\nThese are much more compact but also expensive, compared to the Windmill. \\n\\nTo use them you'll need Water flowing over the Waterwheel. The more Water around it, the faster it'll go. Just make sure the Water isn't flowing in 2 different ways! \\n\\nBeing more compact means we can place 3 Waterwheels on 1 Kinetic Dynamo to get even more Energy.]&f"]
	quest.3DE14F16F3109229.quest_desc: ["通过将任意木材的8块木板与一个&7&a杂酚油桶&f&r结合,我们将得到&a防腐木&f!\\n\\n&a防腐木&f几乎用于&8&l沉浸工程&f&r给我们的每一个物品,以及大多数简单的机器.\\n\\n最重要的是&6工程师装配台&f&r!这些将给我们大量的新配方.\\n&7[By combining 8 Planks of any Wood, with a Bucket of Creosote Oil, we'll get Treated Wood! \\n\\nTreated Wood is used in almost every single Item lIE gives us, plus most of the simple Machines. \\n\\nMost important is the Engineer's Workbenches! These will give us a ton of new Recipes.]&f"]
	quest.3DE14F16F3109229.title: "&a防腐木&f&7[Treated Wood]&f"
	quest.3E32450DBB7529AA.quest_desc: ["&e&a计量分配器&f&r的工作原理有点像过山车的排队线.\\n\\n&a辊压机&f过山车直到所有座位都坐满才会离开!同样,&e计量分配器&r在设定的过滤器和数量匹配之前不会&6输出&r&e物品&r.\\n\\n对于像&5&l&d通用机械&f&r矿石&a处理&f这样需要输入特定数量&e物品&r,否则会造成瓶颈的事情来说非常完美.\\n&7[Item Batcher works kinda like the line for a Roller Coaster. \\n\\nThe Roller Coaster won't leave until all seats are filled! The same way the Batcher won't Output Items until the set Filter and Amount has been matched. \\n\\nPerfect for stuff like lMekanism Ore Processing which needs certain amounts of Items Inputted or else it will bottleneck.]&f"]
	quest.3E32450DBB7529AA.title: "&e&a计量分配器&f&7[Item Batcher]&f"
	quest.3E89034E0CB8D687.quest_desc: ["&a木箱&f的作用类似于桶……但是&2&lMinecraft&r风格的,所以是可以从任何一面打开的箱子!\\n\\n它们有27个槽位,但可以用&6工程师锤&r按住Shift键&a右击&f(多次)来关闭它们!这意味着它们可以被破坏并保留内部的&e物品&r.\\n\\n你还可以编辑箱子的文本来更改其名称,就像在铁砧中一样.\\n\\n&a强化&f箱子的工作原理与普通箱子完全相同,只是不会被炸毁!\\n&7[Wooden Crates act as Barrels... but lMinecraft ones, so Chests that can be opened from any side! \\n\\nThey have 27 Slots but can be Shift Right Clicked with an Engineer's Hammer (multiple times) to shut them closed! This means they can be broken and preserve the Items inside. \\n\\nYou can also edit the Text of the Crate to change its name as if it were in an Anvil. \\n\\nThe Reinforced Crate works exactly the same as the normal one, just can't be blown up!]&f"]
	quest.3E89034E0CB8D687.title: "存储&e物品&7[Storing Items]&f"
	quest.3ED40CC40458087E.quest_desc: ["&c&l&a蓄电池背包&f&r 本身作用不大,我们需要给它安装一个 &c蓄电池&r 才能让它工作!任何 &c蓄电池&r 都行,它不挑剔!\\n\\n在 &6工程师装配台&r 中给它安装一个 &c蓄电池&r 后,你现在就可以给它充电了.充电后,它将为你手持的物品和穿戴的盔甲提供 &c能量&r.\\n\\n你可以通过饰品栏的 &a背部&f 槽位穿戴它,或者放在 &a胸甲&f 槽位,亦或在工作台中与胸甲合成.\\n\\n&a背包&f 可以容纳 1 个 &c蓄电池&r 和 3 个升级组件.\\n&7[The lAccumulator Backpack doesn't do much on your own, we'll need to give it an Accumulator in order to get some work out of it! Any Accumulator it's not judgy! \\n\\nOnce you give it an Accumulator in an Engineer's Workbench, you can now charge it up. Once charged it will provide Energy to Items in your Hand and Armor you are wearing. \\n\\nYou can wear it on your Back Slot in Curios, your Chestplate Slot, or combine it with a Chestplate in a Crafting Table. \\n\\nThe Backpack can hold 1 Accumulator and 3 Upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.3ED40CC40458087E.title: "&c&l&a蓄电池背包&f&7[lAccumulator Backpack]&f"
	quest.3EDDF96EA5056D28.quest_desc: ["&6铜&r 和 &7镍&r 可以制成 &6康铜&r!\\n最后,这种合金在 &8&l沉浸工程&r 中用途相当广泛,尤其是在使用热量和金属的机器或物品中,比如发电机.\\n&7[Copper and Nickel will make Constantan! \\nFinally this one is used quite a bit in lIE, especially in Machines or Items using Heat and Metal, like Generators.]&f"]
	quest.3EDDF96EA5056D28.title: "&6&a康铜锭&f&7[Constantan Ingot]&f"
	quest.3EE95747CA6DFB1A.quest_desc: [
		"&7&l&a金属冲压机&f&r 是所有涉及 &7金属&r 的合成配方的好帮手!\\n\\n操作非常简单:我们将模具放在冲压机上,从顶部接入一些 &c能量&r,然后把我们的 &e物品&r 扔到 &e&a传送带&f&r 上.\\n\\n我们的 &e物品&r 会经过冲压机,被 &7&l冲压&r,然后变成新的 &e物品&r,继续在 &e传送带&r 上移动!\\n\\n这可以用来制作 &c导线&r、&7金属板&r、&8金属杆&r,还有…… &2&a西瓜堆&f&r？\\n&7[The lMetal Press is our Best Friend for all Crafting Recipes with Metal! \\n\\nIt's very simple, we place our Molds onto the Press, attach some Energy to the top, and toss our Items onto the Conveyor Belts. \\n\\nOur Items will pass through, get lPressed, and become a new Item that keeps moving on the Belt! \\n\\nThese can be used to make Wires, Plates, Rods, and... Melon Slices?]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"第一层非常简单,只需要 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 和一个 &4&a红石工程块&f&r 的两侧.\\n&7[First layer is very simple, just Steel Scaffolding and both sides of a Redstone Engineering Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_press1.png width:150 height:75 align:center}"
		"接下来,我们在 &4&a红石工程块&f&r 上方放置一个朝下的活塞,并在其旁边添加两个 &a传送带&f.\\n&7[Next, we place a Piston, facing Down, above the Redstone Engineering Block and add two Conveyor Belts next to it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_press2.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后,在我们的活塞上方放置一个单独的 &7&a重型工程块&f&r!\\n&7[Then, we place a single Heavy Engineering Block above our Piston!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_press3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后,用工程师锤 &a右击&f 活塞!\\n&7[Last, we Right Click the Piston with the Engineer's Hammer!]&f"
	]
	quest.3EE95747CA6DFB1A.title: "&l&7&a金属冲压机&f&7[lMetal Press]&f"
	quest.407C2D00F22BD89D.quest_desc: ["这个升级组件提供了额外 6 发子弹的空间!使总容量达到 14 发.\\n&7[This Upgrade gives space for 6 more Bullets! Making the total up to 14.]&f"]
	quest.4104C5D003D4705A.quest_desc: [
		"另一个使用 &e传送带&r 的多方块结构,我发现规律了.首先,我们需要设置一个 &9蓝图&r.&a右击&f &6&l&a装配机&f&r 打开其 GUI,并将 &9蓝图&r 放入最右侧的槽位.\\n\\n然后,我们的 &e物品&r 可以通过 &e传送带&r 输送,如果配方需要就会被使用.\\n\\n之后,合成好的 &e物品&r(以及不小心放到 &e传送带&r 上的 &e物品&r)会从 &e传送带&r 输出.\\n\\n这对于自动化生产子弹、&0&a高定向热解石墨粉&f&r 和 &7机械零件&r 非常有用.\\n&7[Another Multiblock that uses Belts, I'm seeing a pattern. First, we need to set a Blueprint. Right Click the lAutomated Workbench to open its GUI and place a Blueprint in the Right most slot. \\n\\nThen, we can have our Items go through the Belts to be used in Recipes if possible. \\n\\nAfter that, the Crafted Item (and Items that were accidentally put on the Belts) will go out the Belts. \\n\\nThis is useful for automating Bullets, HOP Graphite, and Mechanical Components.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"我们很多这类结构都以 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 构成的形状开始,这次是一条对角线.在较小的角落,我们将放置一个 &7&a重型工程块&f&r.在较大的角落,我们将放置 2 个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 和一个 &4&a红石工程块&f&r.\\n&7[We start a lot of these with shapes using Steel Scaffolding, this time it is a diagonal line. On the smaller corner we'll place a Heavy Engineering Block. On the bigger corner we'll place 2 Light Engineering Blocks and a Redstone Engineering Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_automated1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"接下来,我们会在它们原来的位置上方放置更多的 &e轻型工程块&r 和 &7&a重型工程块&f&r.在 &4&a红石工程块&f&r 及其 &a左侧&f 的 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 上方,我们将放置 &a防腐木台阶&f.在剩余的空间里,我们将按图示顺序放置 &e&a传送带&f&r.\\n&7[Next, we'll place more Light Engineering and Heavy Engineering Blocks on top of their former selves. Above the Redstone Engineering Block and the Steel Scaffolding to the left of it we'll place Treated Wood Slabs. Within the rest of the space we'll place Conveyor Belts in the order shown.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_automated2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"要获得我们的 &6&l&a装配机&f&r,用 &6工程师锤&r 敲击左侧的 &a防腐木台阶&f!\\n&7[To get our lAutomated Workbench, smack the left Treated Wood Slab with the Engineer's Hammer!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_automated.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4104C5D003D4705A.title: "&l&6&a装配机&f&7[lAutomated Workbench]&f"
	quest.41B99DBD03EB74FF.quest_desc: [
		"相信我,这个多方块结构说它改进了,可不是在说谎!\\n\\n这个结构可以自动化,从顶部接收 &9输入&r,并从正面和 &a背部&f 进行 &6输出&r.\\n\\n此外,我们还可以在它的左右两侧添加预热器!\\n\\n所有这些都使它速度更快,当然,也更高效!\\n&7[Trust me the Multiblock ain't lying when it says it's improved! \\n\\nThis one can be automated to receive Inputs from the Top, and Outputs from the Front and Back Slots. \\n\\nAlso, we can add Preheaters to its Left and Right! \\n\\nAll this makes it much faster and of course, more efficient!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"终于来了个不一样的!你需要先用 &4&a强化高炉砖&f&r 搭建一个 3x3x3 的基座.\\n&7[Finally a different one! You'll start with a base of 3x3x3 Reinforced Blast Bricks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_blast1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_blast2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_blast3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后,在中间方块顶部放置一个漏斗.\\n&7[Then, place a Hopper on the Top of the Middle Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_blast4.png width:100 height:125 align:center}"
		"现在,用 &6工程师锤&r &a右击&f 第二层的中间 &a方块&f.\\n&7[Now Right Click the Middle Block of the 2nd layer with the Engineer's Hammer.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_blast.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.41B99DBD03EB74FF.title: "&l&4&a强化高炉&f&7[lImproved Blast Furnace]&f"
	quest.4295C863C9A81F28.quest_desc: ["特斯拉线圈是一个非常有趣且 &c耗能&r 巨大的家园防御装置!\\n\\n首先,通过其任意端口提供 &c能量&r.然后,要么给它一个 &4&a红石信号&f&r 来开启它,要么使用 &6工程师螺丝刀&r 让它保持常开!\\n\\n一旦开启,它会持续消耗 &c能量&r,当有生物靠近时,它会击晕并伤害它们!不过,伤害生物会消耗更多 &c能量&r.\\n\\n你可以按住 Shift 并用 &6工程师螺丝刀&r &a右击&f 来将其设置为低功耗模式.这样它会消耗更少的 &c能量&r,但范围也会变小,造成的 &a伤害&f 也更低!\\n&7[The Telsa Coil is a very fun and Energy hungry home defence! \\n\\nFirst, power it with Energy from any of its Ports. Then, either give it a Redstone Signal to turn it on, or use a Engineer's Screwdriver to make it always on! \\n\\nOnce it is on it will be actively using Energy and when a Mob comes near it, it will Stun them and hurt them! Hurting Mobs makes it take more Energy though. \\n\\nYou can Shift Right Click with an Engineer's Screwdriver to set it to low power mode. It will take less Energy but also have less Range and deal less Damage!]&f"]
	quest.431C62A6F8ECB4EC.quest_desc: ["&7&a铝杆&f&r - 10 \\n&7&a铁杆&f&r - 16 \\n&8&a钢杆&f&r - 24 \\n&8锯片&r - 12 \\n&0&a石墨电极&f&r - 30\\n&7[Aluminum Rod - 10 \\nIron Rod - 16 \\nSteel Rod - 24 \\nSawblade - 12 \\nGraphite Electrode - 30]&f"]
	quest.431C62A6F8ECB4EC.title: "来自 &8&l沉浸工程&r 的 &5&l磁轨炮&r 弹药&7[lRailgun Ammo from lIE]&f"
	quest.442B1A1900BADAFC.quest_desc: ["&8&l沉浸工程&r 中的一些机器不是多方块结构,而是单方块机器!\\n\\n不过,别因为它们只用 1 个方块制成,就认为它们不重要!\\n&7[Some Machines in lIE aren't Multiblocks, rather they are single-blocked! \\n\\nDon't think that, just because they are made with 1 Block that, they aren't important though! ]&f"]
	quest.442B1A1900BADAFC.title: "小型机器&7[Small Machines]&f"
	quest.452EF09F6CB4AD99.quest_desc: ["&c中继器&r 不将 &c导线&r 连接到机器,而是将 &c导线&r 连接到更多的 &c导线&r!\\n\\n&c中继器&r 的工作原理是将一堆 &c导线&r 汇集到一个点,因此它会接收所有 &9输入&r 的 &c能量&r,并通过 &c连接器&r 发送给所有连接的 &6输出&r.\\n\\n当你有一个发电机想给多个机器充电时,这很有帮助!\\n&7[Relays don't connect Wires to Machines, rather they connect Wires to more Wires! \\n\\nRelays work by combining a bunch of Wires into one spot, so it will take all the Input Energy and send them to Connectors to all the Outputs connected. \\n\\nThis is helpful for when you have either one Power Generator that you want to charge multiple Machines!]&f"]
	quest.452EF09F6CB4AD99.title: "&c中继器&7[Relays]&f"
	quest.458265FCD6B3068E.quest_desc: ["大家都喜欢 &l匠魂&r 的合成站,显然 &8&l沉浸工程&r 的开发者们也一样!\\n\\n&6工程师装配台&r 就像一个普通的工作台,但额外增加了 18 个存储槽位,而且当你停止查看它时,它会保留你放在合成网格里的 &e物品&r!\\n\\n你还能要求什么呢!\\n&7[Everybody loved the Crafting Stations from lTinker's Construct and apparently so did the lIE Devs! \\n\\nThe Engineer's Crafting Table will act like a normal Crafting Table, with an added 18 Slots of Storage in it, plus it keeps your Items in the Grid when you stop viewing it! \\n\\nWhat more could you want!]&f"]
	quest.458265FCD6B3068E.title: "&6工程师装配台&7[Engineer's Crafting Table]&f"
	quest.47656073894224AF.quest_desc: ["是的,它就像那些巨型战舰上的一样!\\n\\n&5&l磁轨炮&r 是一种特殊的枪.首先,它使用特殊弹药,而不是像左轮手枪那样使用弹壳；其次,它使用 &c能量&r 并且射击前需要充能.\\n\\n它使用的弹药是你物品栏中的 &e物品&r:&7铝&r、&7铁&r 和 &8&a钢杆&f&r、&0&a石墨电极&f&r、锯片、末影珍珠、三叉戟、&a烈焰棒&f 和 &a末地烛&f.\\n\\n它会使用你物品栏中的任何东西,要改变射击的弹药,请 &a按住 Shift 键&f 并滚动滚轮.\\n\\n接下来,它需要内部有 &c能量&r 才能射击,我们可以使用任何 &c物品充能器&r 给它充电,包括 &8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r 添加的那个!\\n\\n一旦我们准备好这一切,按住 &a右键&f 直到磁轨炮充能达到 99 级,然后松开!\\n\\n&5&l磁轨炮&r 的升级组件有:&a瞄准镜&f 和散热片.\\n\\n它可以容纳 2 个升级组件,嗯,这很合理,它用不了更多了!\\n&7[Yes, it is just like the ones on giant Battleships! \\n\\nThe lRailgun is a special Gun. For 1. it uses special Ammo, not Cartridges like the Revolver uses 2. it uses Energy and needs to charge before shooting. \\n\\nThe Ammo it uses is Items from your Inventory: Aluminum, Iron, and Steel Rods, Graphite Electrodes, Sawblades, Enderpearls, Tridents, Blaze Rods, and End Rods. \\n\\nIt'll take whatever is in your Inventory, to change what it Shoots, Hold Shift and Scroll. \\n\\nNext, it needs Energy within it to Shoot, to charge it we can use any Item Charger, including the one added by lImmersive Engineering! \\n\\nOnce we have all this, Hold Right Click until the Railgun gets to Level 99, then release! \\n\\nThe lRailgun's Upgrades are: Precision Scope and Heatsinks. \\n\\nIt can hold 2 Upgrades, well that makes sense it can't use anymore than that!]&f"]
	quest.47656073894224AF.title: "&5&l磁轨炮&7[lRailgun]&f"
	quest.47E32A084CAA1512.quest_desc: ["可以与军械师交易或合成获得.\\n\\n没有子弹的枪可没什么意思,所以让我们合成一些吧!不过要合成它们,我们需要这个 &9蓝图&r.\\n&7[Can be Traded with a Gunsmith or Crafted. \\n\\nGuns aren't much fun without Bullets, so let's Craft some! In order to Craft them though we'll need this Blueprint.]&f"]
	quest.47E32A084CAA1512.title: "&9&a普通子弹&f 蓝图&7[Common Projectiles Blueprint]&f"
	quest.481735FE3164C8D5.quest_desc: ["&b&a蓝冰&f&r - 200 K \\n&b&a浮冰&f&r - 240 K \\n&b冰&r - 260 K \\n雪 - 273 K \\n&9水&r - 300 K\\n&7[Blue Ice- 200 K \\nPacked Ice- 240 K \\nIce- 260 K \\nSnow- 273 K \\nWater- 300]&f"]
	quest.481735FE3164C8D5.title: "&b寒冷物品&7[Cold Items]&f"
	quest.4AAB3899F530CC19.quest_desc: ["滑槽可以接收 &e物品&r(和一些实体)并将其丢下,不用担心它们会消失!\\n\\n它们掉落 &e物品&r 的速度也非常快.\\n\\n你可以使用 &6工程师锤&r 让滑槽弯曲,从而将 &e物品&r 抛到 &e传送带&r 上!\\n&7[Chutes can take Items (and some Entities) and drop them without worry of despawning! \\n\\nThey also drop Items pretty darn quickly. \\n\\nYou can use the Engineer's Hammer to make a Chute curve to toss the Items onto a Belt!]&f"]
	quest.4AAB3899F530CC19.quest_subtitle: "没有梯子？&7[No Ladders?]&f"
	quest.4B42D962FE910CB3.quest_desc: ["将这个升级组件安装到你的 &d&l左轮手枪&r 上后,你的子弹会给击中的生物施加击晕效果.\\n&7[With this added on to your lRevolver, your Bullets will give the Mobs you hit the Stunned Effect.]&f"]
	quest.4BA2F4AC2A08C294.quest_desc: [
		"那是什么？那可是 &8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r 中最难建造、最昂贵的多方块结构.&c&l挖掘机&r!\\n\\n这个庞然大物会自动从地下收集矿石和方块.\\n\\n它拾取的物品会从其背部的端口 &6输出&r.如果旁边没有容器,它会将物品直接弹出.\\n\\n这也是一个超级 &c耗能&r 的机器,你需要使用它左侧的能量端口来给它供能!\\n&7[What's that? It's only the hardest and most expensive Multiblock in lImmersive Engineering. The lExcavator! \\n\\nThis giant behemoth will automatically collect Ores and Blocks from the Ground. \\n\\nThe Items it picks up will be Output from a Port in the Back of it. If there's no Inventory next to it, it will dispense the Items. \\n\\nThis is also a super Energy hungry Machine, you'll need to use the Energy Ports on the Left Side of it to feed it!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"放置一个 &8&a钢块&f&r.\\n&7[Place a Steel Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"在 &8&a钢块&f&r 上方添加 3 个 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r,并在两端各放置 2 个 &8&a钢块&f&r.\\n&7[Add 3 Steel Scaffolding above the Steel Block and place 2 Steel Blocks on the ends.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator2.png width:175 height:100 align:center}"
		"之后,在之前的 &8脚手架&r 上方放置一个 3x3 的 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r,并在每个 &8&a钢块&f&r 上额外放一个.然后,使用 &8&a钢板金属块&f&r 在 &8脚手架&r 外围做一个环,包括一个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 和一个 &8&a散热器模块&f&r.\\n&7[After that place a 3x3 of Steel Scaffolding above the previous Scaffolding, and an extra one on each of the Steel Blocks. Then, using Steel Sheetmetal make a hoop off of the Scaffolding, including a Light Engineering Block and a Radiator Block. ]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator3.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"在 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 上方添加更多,中间放一个 &8&a钢块&f&r.然后,在那些脚手架的末端再连接一些 &8&a钢块&f&r.一边是 3 个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r,另一边是 3 个 &7&a重型工程块&f&r.在最后一层的 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 上方,再放一个.在 &8&a散热器模块&f&r 上方,放一个 &4&a红石工程块&f&r.旁边再放一个 &7&a重型工程块&f&r,其余部分用 &8&a钢板金属块&f&r 填充.\\n&7[Above the Steel Scaffolding add more, with a Steel Block in the middle. Then, attach more Steel Blocks to the ends of those. On one side it'll be 3 Light Engineering Blocks and the other will be 3 Heavy Engineering Blocks. Above the Light Engineering Block in the last layer, will be another. And above the Radiator Block will be a Redstone Engineering Block. Next to it will be another Heavy Engineering Block and the rest will be Steel Sheetmetal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator4.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"现在中间部分我们将重复下半部分的做法,所以现在只是 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r.在 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 旁边的侧面,再放 3 个,另一侧那个随机的 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 旁边也一样.3 个 &e&a轻型工程块&f&r 旁边是 2 个 &8&a散热器模块&f&r,其余部分都是 &8钢板金属块&r.\\n&7[Now for the middle part we'll be repeating what we did below the half, so now it's just Steel Scaffolding. On the side next to it with Light Engineering Blocks will be 3 more, same with the random Light Engineering Block on the otherside. Next to the 3 Light Engineering Blocks will be 2 Radiator Blocks, and everything else is Sheetmetal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator5.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"在 &8&a钢脚手架&f&r 上方,将是 1 个 &8&a钢块&f&r,接着是 3 个 &8脚手架&r 和另一个 &8方块&r.\\n&7[Above the Steel Scaffolding will be 1 Steel Block followed by 3 Scaffolding and another Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator6.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后画龙点睛的一笔,&8&a钢块&f&r!\\n&7[The final cherry on top, Steel Block!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator7.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后,我们只需用 &6工程师锤&r &a右击&f 后面的 &7&a重型工程块&f&r,它就会变成强大的 &c&l挖掘机&r!\\n&7[Then, we just Right Click the Heavy Engineering Block in the back with our Hammer and it'll become the mighty lExcavator!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_excavator.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4BA2F4AC2A08C294.title: "&l&c挖掘机&7[lExcavator]&f"
	quest.4BBF987FEF639801.quest_desc: [
		"合金是两种不同金属的组合.\\n\\n金属通常在室温下不是液态,所以我们需要稍微熔炼它们(感谢水银!).\\n\\n将两种金属放入顶部的槽位,将像 &0木炭&r 这样的熔炉燃料放入底部的槽位.\\n\\n等等…… &8钢&r 是一种合金!\\n&7[Alloys are combinations of 2 different Metals. \\n\\nMetals aren't usually liquid at room temperature so we'll need to smelt them a bit (thanks Mercury)! \\n\\nAdd the 2 Metals into the top slots, and a Furnace Fuel like Charcoal into the bottom slot. \\n\\nWait... Steel is an Alloy!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&6&l&a合金窑&f&r 是一个由 &6&a窑砖&f&r 构成的 2x2x2 结构.\\n&7[The lAlloy Kiln is a 2x2x2 of Kiln Bricks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_alloy1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_alloy2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后用 &6工程师锤&r &a右击&f &a右上角&f 的方块来制造它!\\n&7[Then Right Click the Top Right Block with an Engineer's Hammer to make it!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_alloy.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4BBF987FEF639801.title: "&l&6&a合金窑&f&7[lAlloy Kiln]&f"
	quest.4C4C9ADAC6107F89.quest_desc: ["&e&a轻型工程块&f&r的配方相当简单.\\n\\n你需要1个&6&a铜锭&f&r,这个我不用解释,它完全是&2&l原版&r的特性.\\n\\n4个&7铁板&r,就是4个&7&a铁板&f&r互相组合!\\n\\n你还需要4个&7&a铁质机械零件&f&r,它们可以在工作台中用4个&7&a铁板&f&r和1个&6&a铜锭&f&r合成,或者在&6工程师装配台&r中用2个&7&a铁板&f&r和1个&6&a铜锭&f&r合成.\\n&7[The Light Engineering Block is pretty easy recipe. \\n\\nYou'll need 1 Copper Ingot, which I shouldn't have to explain it's literally a lVanilla feature. \\n\\n4 Ironsheetmetal, which are just 4 Iron Plates combined with each other! \\n\\nYou'll also need 4 Iron Mechanical Components, which are either 4 Iron Plates and a Copper Ingot in a Crafting Table, or 2 Iron Plates and a Copper Ingot in the Engineer's Workbench.]&f"]
	quest.4C4C9ADAC6107F89.title: "&e&a轻型工程块&f&7[Light Engineering Block]&f"
	quest.4D193D60A3CAF435.quest_desc: [
		"这是你最可能使用的发电机,&2&l&a柴油发电机&f!\\n\\n你将在&2&l&a柴油发电机&f的底部左右角落&9输入&r燃料.燃料可以是:杂酚油、生物柴油和&a高十六烷值生物柴油&f.这些按从最差到最好的顺序排列!\\n\\n&2&l&a柴油发电机&f会燃烧燃料并产生&c能量&r,这些能量可以从前面的3个连接器&6输出&r.\\n&7[This is the Generator you will most likely be using, the lDiesel Generator! \\n\\nYou will Input Fuel in the bottom left and right corners of the lDiesel Generator. The Fuel can be: Creasote Oil, Biodiesel, and High-Cetane Biodiesel. Those are in order from worst to best! \\n\\nThe lDiesel Generator will burn the Fuel and produce Energy which can be Output from the 3 connectors in the front.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"在&2&l&a柴油发电机&f的背面,我们需要3个&8&a散热器模块&f&r.中间将是&b&a流体传输管道&f&r,周围是&8&a钢脚手架&f&r.前面有一个&6&a发电机模块&f&r,旁边是2个&b&a流体传输管道&f&r.\\n&7[In the back of the lDiesel Generator we'll need 3 Radiator Blocks. The middle will be Fluid Pipes surrounded by Steel Scaffolding. With the front having a Generator Block and 2 Fluid Pipes next to it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_diesel1.png width:100 height:150 align:center}"
		"在3个&8&a散热器模块&f&r上方,还有另外3个&8&a散热器模块&f&r!而旁边的&6&a发电机模块&f&r和&b&a流体传输管道&f&r,上方将有3个&6&a发电机模块&f&r.其余部分将用&7&a重型工程块&f&r和单个&4&a红石工程块&f&r填充.\\n&7[Above the 3 Radiator Blocks will be 3 more Radiator Blocks! And the Generator Block and Fluid Pipes next to it, will have 3 Generator Blocks above them. The rest will be filled with Heavy Engineering Blocks and a single Redstone Engineering Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_diesel2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后我们还需要3个&8&a散热器模块&f&r放在其他模块的上方,并在其旁边用&7&a重型工程块&f&r摆成一个十字形.\\n&7[To finish we'll need 3 more Radiator Blocks above the other ones, and next to it we'll make a cross of Heavy Engineering Blocks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_diesel3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后一步是用我们的&6工程师锤&f&r&a右击&f中间和顶部的&6&a发电机模块&f&r!\\n&7[Last step is to Right Click the middle and top Generator Block with our Engineer's Hammer!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_diesel.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4D193D60A3CAF435.title: "&2&l&a柴油发电&f&7[lDiesel Generator]&f"
	quest.4D8190E94851C546.quest_desc: ["通电的&c导线&f(传输&c能量&f的&c导线&f即为通电&c导线&f)在你使用&6&l天钩&f&r时会对你造成伤害.\\n\\n除非你给握柄做了绝缘!\\n&7[Live Wires (Wires transporting Energy are Live Wires) will hurt you when using a lSkyhook on them. \\n\\nUnless you Insulate your Grip!]&f"]
	quest.4E297778DCEEC963.quest_desc: ["&a附加电容&f是我们&5&l磁轨炮&f&r独有的升级.\\n\\n它能让&5&l磁轨炮&f&r充能快得多!\\n&7[Advanced Heatsinks are our only lRailgun exclusive Upgrades. \\n\\nIt will make it so the lRailgun charges up much faster!]&f"]
	quest.4F56BFE6E4716F6D.quest_desc: [
		"&8&l&a电弧炉&f&r是一个庞大且有用的机器.它让大多数其他机器都变得无用!\\n\\n首先,你需要从&8&l&a电弧炉&f&r背面的接口输入&c能量&f.然后它需要燃料,即&0&a石墨电极&f&r.这些只能放入其GUI中,无法自动化.\\n\\n接着,你需要将&e物品&f&6输入&f到顶部端口,靠近&0&a石墨电极&f&r的地方.当有燃料和能量时,它几乎能熔化任何东西.从&7&a铁棒&f&r到&7&a铁锭&f&r,从&b&a霜钢头盔&f&r到&b霜钢&f&r,从&e金镐&f&r到&e金&f&r!\\n\\n熔化后的&e物品&f会&6输出&f到背面电源接口下方的位置.\\n\\n它还能用金属制造合金!\\n&7[The lArc Furnace is a massive and helpful Machine. It makes most other Machines useless! \\n\\nTo start you'll need Energy Input from the outlets in the Back of the lArc Furnace. It'll then need Fuel which are Graphite Electrodes. These can only be placed into its GUI, they can't be automated. \\n\\nYou'll then need to Input the Items into the Top Ports, near where the Graphite Electrodes are. When fueled and powered it'll melt down, just about anything. From Iron Rods to Iron Ingots, to Froststeel Helmets to Froststeel, to Gold Pickaxes to Gold! \\n\\nThe melted down Items will be Output into the Back below the Power Outlets. \\n\\nIt can also make Alloys from Metals!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"第一层先用&8&a钢板金属块&f&r摆成一个U形,中心是&7&a重型工程块&f&r,两端是&8&a钢块&f&r.其余部分用&8&a钢板台阶&f&r填充,外加一个单独的&8&a钢脚手架&f&r和一个炼药锅.\\n&7[1st layer starts off with a U made of Steel Sheetmetal with the center being Heavy Engineering Block and the tips being Steel Blocks. The rest will be Steel Sheetmetal Slabs with a stray Steel Scaffolding and Cauldron.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_arc1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"第二层,在&7&a重型工程块&f&r及其两侧的方块上方放置&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.然后,U形的两侧用&7&a重型工程块&f&r.在之前的&8&a钢块&f&r上方放置更多&8&a钢块&f&r.我们还需要在&8台阶&f&r上方放置一个2x3的&4&a强化高炉砖&f&r.别忘了在&8脚手架&f&r上方放一个&4&a红石工程块&f&r!\\n&7[2nd layer starts with, above the Heavy Engineering Block and the 2 Blocks next to it will be Light Engineering Blocks. Then, the sides of the U will be Heavy Engineering Blocks. With more Steel Blocks above the previous ones. We'll also need a 2x3 of Reinforced Blast Bricks above the Slabs. Don't forget the Redstone Engineering Block above the Scaffolding!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_arc2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"第三层需要更多&8&a钢块&f&r,更多&e&a轻型工程块&f&r,并延伸我们的&4&a强化高炉砖&f&r.我们还需要在每侧各放1个&8&a钢板金属块&f&r.\\n&7[3rd has more Steel Blocks, more Light Engineering Blocks, and an extension of our Reinforced Blast Bricks. We'll also need 1 Steel Sheetmetal on each side.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_arc3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"第四层需要在中间其他方块的上方放置一个&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.其旁边将是2个&8&a钢脚手架&f&r.我们还需要添加更多&4&a强化高炉砖&f&r,但这次要短&a一&f格!\\n&7[4th needs a Light Engineering Block placed in the middle above the others. Next to it will be 2 Steel Scaffolding. And we'll need to add more Reinforced Blast Brick but this time a Block of length short!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_arc4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"第五层即最后一层,只需在之前的方块上再放2个&8&a钢脚手架&f&r.然后,在之前那个方块的上方及其前方一排放置&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.\\n&7[5th and final layer is just 2 more Steel Scaffolding on top of the others. Then, Light Engineering Blocks above the previous one and in a line in front of it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_arc5.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"最后用&6锤子&f&r&a右击&f炼药锅来完成它!\\n&7[Finally Right Click the Cauldron with the Hammer to finish it!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_arc.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4F56BFE6E4716F6D.title: "&8&l&a电弧炉&f&7[lArc Furnace]&f"
	quest.50326B1D6EE8FA0B.quest_desc: ["&c蓄电池&f&r是&8&lIE&f&r的电池版本.\\n\\n它们储存&c能量&f,&6低压&f蓄电池储存100kFE,&e中压&f蓄电池储存1MFE,&5高压&f蓄电池储存4MFE!\\n\\n默认情况下,它们有一个顶部槽位仅允许&9输入&f,但任何侧面都可以用&6工程师锤&f&r更改为&9输入&f、&6输出&f或两者都不是.\\n&7[Accumulators are lIE's version of batteries. \\n\\nThey hold Energy with LV holding 100kFE, MV holds 1MFE, and HV holds 4MFE! \\n\\nBy default they have a top slot which only allows Input, but any side can be changed with the Engineer's Hammer to Input, Output, or Neither.]&f"]
	quest.50326B1D6EE8FA0B.title: "&c蓄电池&7[Accumulators]&f"
	quest.506F20AF8E857559.quest_desc: ["&a动能发电机&f是一种利用动量产生能量的发电机!\\n\\n要开始产生能量,你需要在侧面那个有巨大开口的洞上连接一个水车或风车!\\n\\n&a动能发电机&f没有内部能量存储,而是向连接的方块(如连接器或蓄电池)提供能量.\\n&7[The Kinetic Dynamo is a Generator which uses momentum to make Energy! \\n\\nTo start making Energy you'll need either a Waterwheel or Windmill attached to the side with the giant gaping hole in it! \\n\\nThe Kinetic Dynamo doesn't have an internal Energy storage, rather it provides Energy to connected Blocks like Connectors or Accumulators.]&f"]
	quest.506F20AF8E857559.title: "来自运动物体的能量!&7[Energy from moving things!]&f"
	quest.50F1C4521D282C60.quest_desc: ["&a身如壁垒&f是这些武装分子的重型单位.\\n\\n它们有12颗心,外加18点&a护甲值&f!\\n\\n他们的武器是&b&l化学喷射器&f&r,副手拿着&8&l&a重型盾牌&f&r.\\n\\n如果你设法杀死一个,你将获得&a绿宝石&f和大师级着色器袋!\\n&7[The Bulwark are the heavy units of these militants. \\n\\nThey have 12 Hearts with 18 Armor Points! \\n\\nTheir weapon is the lChemthrower with a lHeavy Plated Shield in the Offhand. \\n\\nIf you somehow kill one you will get Emeralds and Masterwork Shader Bags!]&f"]
	quest.50F1C4521D282C60.title: "身如壁垒&7[Bulwark]&f"
	quest.520904C106D7D93D.quest_desc: ["这些升级让&6&l天钩&f&r表现得类似钉头锤,如果你在下落时击中生物,会造成额外的&a伤害&f.\\n\\n在《生化奇兵:无限》中,这被称为天袭!\\n&7[These make the lSkyhook act similar to a Mace, you'll do extra Damage hurting Mobs if you are falling while you hit them. \\n\\nIn Bioshock Infinite it's called a Skystrike!]&f"]
	quest.520904C106D7D93D.quest_subtitle: "按下左键发动天袭&7[Press LMB to Skystrike]&f"
	quest.5218DAE147AC9F44.quest_desc: ["&a锯片盒子&f允许你在&2&l电锯&f&r上存放更多&8锯片&f&r或&8类锯片物品&f&r.\\n\\n要在&8锯片&f&r(或&8类锯片物品&f&r)之间切换,请&a按下Shift键&f并滚动滚轮.\\n\\n这对于更换损坏的&8锯片&f&r,甚至切换到&8磨盘&f&r很有用!\\n&7[The Blade Quiver allows you to hold more Blades or Blade like Items on the lBuzzsaw. \\n\\nTo switch between the Blades (or Blade like Items) Hold Shift and Scroll. \\n\\nThis is useful for replacing broken Blades or even switching to Grinding Disks!]&f"]
	quest.553ADA7040B652CD.quest_desc: ["&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r、&2&l电锯&f&r和&b&l&a化学喷射器&f&r通常可容纳1,000mB或&a1桶&f的&b流体&f.\\n\\n通常不代表总是!使用&a大型油箱&f后,它们现在可以容纳2,000mB或&a2桶&f的量.\\n\\n听起来可能不多,但相信我,这很重要.\\n&7[The lMining Drill, lBuzzsaw, and lChemical Thrower normally hold 1,000mB or 1 Bucket worth of Fluid. \\n\\nNormally doesn't mean always! With the Large Tank they can now hold 2,000mB or 2 Buckets worth. \\n\\nIt doesn't sound like a lot but trust me it is.]&f"]
	quest.5585130028BB8298.quest_desc: ["我们在&6&lATM10&f&r能找到的最基本的枪,&d&l左轮手枪&f&r!\\n\\n按住Shift并&a右击打开&f&d&l左轮手枪&f&r,然后将一些弹药移动到槽位中.之后,只需&a右击&f即可射击!\\n\\n你可以为其应用2个升级.&a新材料发现&f包括:刺刀、快速装弹器、&a扩充弹夹&f、&a加强电子管&f和&a瞄准镜&f.\\n\\n&d&l左轮手枪&f&r只能容纳2个升级,但快速装弹器在技术上有所不同.\\n&7[The most basic Gun we can find in lATM10, the lRevolver! \\n\\nShift Right Click to open the lRevolver, then move some Ammo into the Slots. After that, just Right Click to shoot! \\n\\nYou can apply 2 Upgrades to it. The Upgrades being: Bayonet, Speedloader, Extended Magazine, Amplifier Electron Tubes, and Precision Scope. \\n\\nThe lRevolver can only hold 2 Upgrades but the Speedloader is technically different.]&f"]
	quest.5585130028BB8298.quest_subtitle: "你觉得幸运吗,小子？&7[Do you feel lucky, Punk?]&f"
	quest.5585130028BB8298.title: "&d&l左轮手枪&7[lRevolver]&f"
	quest.56CE6CF9C99FB522.quest_desc: ["对于&8散热器&f&r,我们需要常用的&8&a钢板金属块&f&r,一个&9&a水桶&f&r(这是新东西!)以及&6&a康铜板&f&r.\\n\\n&6康铜&f&r是一种合金,通过在&l&6&a合金窑&f&r中结合&6铜&f&r和&7镍&f&r制成.\\n&7[For Radiators we'll need the usual Steel Sheetmetal, a Water Bucket which is a new one! And Constantan Plates. \\n\\nConstantan is an Alloy made by combining Copper and Nickel in an lAlloy Kiln.]&f"]
	quest.56CE6CF9C99FB522.title: "&8&a散热器模块&f&7[Radiator Block]&f"
	quest.56E30438AE512475.quest_desc: ["让我们点燃这些火焰!\\n\\n预热器是&l&4&a强化高炉&f&r的一个非常简单的附加装置.\\n\\n只需将它们放置在&l&4&a强化高炉&f&r的左侧和右侧.然后,从顶部连接能量,它就会开始加速&l&4&a强化高炉&f&r的进程.\\n&7[Let's get these flames burning! \\n\\nThe Preheater is a very simple addition to the lImproved Blast Furnace. \\n\\nSimply place them on the Left and Right of the lImproved Blast Furnace. Then, connect power to the top of it and it will start speeding up the lImproved Blast Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.573C2242EAB85B49.quest_desc: [
		"&0&l&a焦炉&f&r是我们制造&0&a焦煤&f&r的方式,猜猜它用什么做的!\\n\\n我们可以用&0&l焦炉&f&r将原木烧制成&0木炭&f&r,或者将&0煤炭&f&r和&0煤炭块&f&r烧制成&0焦煤&f&r!\\n\\n这两种方法除了正常产物外,还会产生&a杂酚油&f.\\n&7[lCoke Oven is how we make our Coal Coke, take a guess what it's made of! \\n\\nWe can use the lOven to smelt Logs into Charcoal, or smelt Coal and Coal Blocks into Coke! \\n\\nEither of these will produce Creosote Oil as well as the normal recipe.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&0&l&a焦炉&f&r是一个非常简单的多方块结构,由&0&a焦炉砖&f&r构成3x3x3的立方体.\\n&7[The lCoke Oven is a very simple Multiblock, 3x3x3 of Coke Bricks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_coke1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_coke2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_coke3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"只需用&6工程师锤&f&r&a右击&f中间&a方块&f的&a正面&f即可创建它.\\n&7[Simply Right Click the Middle Block of the Front Side with an Engineer's Hammer to create it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_coke.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.573C2242EAB85B49.title: "&l&8&a焦炉&f&7[lCoke Oven]&f"
	quest.586F6FD38CF85DCA.quest_desc: ["&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r如其名,用于采矿!\\n\\n它像&a镐子&f一样工作,只需要&8&a钻头&f&r和&2生物柴油&f&r.&8&a钻头&f&r决定其挖掘等级并具有耐久度,这意味着需要更换.你可以在&6工程师装配台&f&r的顶部槽位安装&8&a钻头&f&r.\\n\\n&2生物柴油&f&r是一种&b液体燃料&f&r,其配方非常难制作……不过那是另一个任务的内容,我们现在只关心如何给它加燃料!你可以将&4&l钻头&f&r对准任何装有&2生物柴油&f&r的&b储罐&f&r或机器来填充它.\\n\\n&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r会以3x3或2x2的区域采矿,除非你在破坏时按住Shift!\\n\\n你也可以用它攻击生物,造成与&a下界合金剑&f相同的&a伤害&f,但这会消耗燃料和耐久度.\\n\\n&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&r可以容纳1个&a钻头&f和3个升级.\\n&7[The lMining Drill does as the name suggests, it Mines! \\n\\nIt works like a Pickaxe, just needing Drill Heads and Bio-Diesel. Drill Heads determine its Mining Level and have Durability which means they'll need to be replaced. You can attach Drill Heads in the Engineer's Workbench, in the Top Slot. \\n\\nBio-Diesel is a Liquid Fuel which has a very difficult recipe to make... that's for a different Quest though we're just looking for how to Fuel it! You can use the lDrill on any Tank or Machine holding Bio-Diesel to fill it. \\n\\nThe lMining Drill will mine in a 3x3 or 2x2 area, unless you are Shifting while breaking! \\n\\nYou can also Hit Mobs with it to do the same amount of Damage as a Netherite Sword, this takes up Fuel as well as Durability though. \\n\\nThe lMining Drill can hold 1 Drill Head and 3 Upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.586F6FD38CF85DCA.quest_subtitle: "你愿意帮个忙吗？&7[Would you kindly?]&f"
	quest.586F6FD38CF85DCA.title: "&4&l&a采矿钻头&f&7[lMining Drill]&f"
	quest.591E6964ABCC638C.quest_desc: ["&e&a传送带&f&r是我们移动&e物品&f&r(和一些实体)的方式.\\n\\n当&e物品&f&r掉落到&e传送带&f&r上时,传送带会托住并移动它们.然后这些物品可以被移入不同的容器.如果我们想从容器中提取物品,则需要一种特殊类型的&e传送带&f&r!\\n\\n你放置&e传送带&f&r的方式将决定其移动方向,这也可以用&6工程师锤&f&r改变!\\n它们需要放置在方块上,但有趣的是,下方不需要有方块支撑也能保持站立和工作!\\n&7[Conveyor Belts are how we can move Items (and some Entities). \\n\\nWhen Items are dropped onto Belts they will hold them and move them. These can then be moved into different Inventories, if we want to extract from Inventories we'll need a special type of Belt! \\n\\nThe way you place your Belt will determine where it moves, this can also be changed with the Engineer's Hammer! \\nThey need to be placed on Blocks but funny enough don't need Blocks below to keep standing and working!]&f"]
	quest.591E6964ABCC638C.quest_subtitle: "和一些实体!&7[and some Entities!]&f"
	quest.591E6964ABCC638C.title: "移动&e物品&f&7[Moving Items]&f"
	quest.598DE7CEDA864B50.quest_desc: ["既然能用3个,为什么只用1个油箱!\\n\\n你现在可以在&b&l&a化学喷射器&f&r中存放3种不同的&b流体&f&r.&a按下Shift键&f并滚动滚轮可在它们之间&a切换模式&f.\\n\\n不过这不能与&a大型油箱&f一起使用……\\n&7[Why just have 1 Tank, when we can use 3! \\n\\nYou can now hold 3 different Fluids in your lChemical Thrower. Hold Shift and Scroll to switch between them. \\n\\nThis can't be used with the Large Tank though...]&f"]
	quest.5A2A718C569F3C19.quest_desc: ["通过在&l&a焦炉&f&r中烧炼&0煤炭&f&r,我们可以得到&0&a焦煤&f&r!或者我称之为&0焦煤&f&r!\\n\\n它基本上就是&0煤炭&f&r,但在&8&lIE&f&r中有更多用途.\\n\\n你可以将其与铁结合得到&7钢&f&r,粉碎它得到&0&a焦煤粉&f&r(这是制造&0石墨&f&r所需的),或者用作&a爆裂熔炉&f的燃料.\\n&7[By Smelting Coal in a lCoke Oven we can get Coal Coke! Or as I will call it, just Coke! \\n\\nIt pretty much is just Coal but has more uses in lIE. \\n\\nYou can combine it with Iron to get Steel, Crush it to get Coke Dust which will be needed for Graphite, or use as Fuel for a Blast Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.5A2A718C569F3C19.title: "&8焦煤&f&7[Coke]&f"
	quest.5C5546A5103BCF55.quest_desc: ["这东西本应喷射像&b流体&f&r或气体这样的化学品……但它对我没用.\\n\\n它至少能容纳2个升级!那些是有效的!\\n&7[This one is supposed to shoot Chemicals like Fluids or Gases... but it won't do it for me. \\n\\nIt can hold 2 Upgrades atleast! Those work!]&f"]
	quest.5C5546A5103BCF55.title: "&b&l&a化学喷射器&f&7[lChemical Thrower]&f"
	quest.5DE3F2A96715BA2E.quest_desc: [
		"&e&l筒仓&f&r是一个多方块结构,用于存储大量单一类型的&e物品&f&r,就像一个抽屉.\\n\\n你可以通过&a顶部&f或&a底部&f&9存入&f该&e物品&f&r及其同类物品,但要&6提取&f,你需要使用&a底部&f!\\n\\n它可以容纳41,472个&e物品&f&r,但只能是同一种类型.\\n&7[The lSilo is a Multiblock made for storing tons of just one type of Item, like a Drawer. \\n\\nYou can deposit the Item and its duplicates in the Top Side or Bottom Side, but to extract you'll need to use the Bottom Side! \\n\\nIt can hold 41,472 Items, just only of the same type.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"首先,我们放置一个由&a防腐木栅栏&f围成的正方形,中心放一个&7&a铁板&f金属块&f&r.\\n&7[First we place a square of Treated Wood Fences with an Iron Sheetmetal in the center.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo1.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"接下来,在我们的栅栏上方用&7&a铁板&f金属块&f&r摆成一个完整的正方形,同时中心留空.重复此步骤5次!\\n&7[Next, we make a full square of Iron Sheetmetal above our Fences, while leaving a space in the center hollow. Do this 5 times!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo5.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo6.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后,最后一层是整个&7&a铁板&f金属块&f&r的正方形,包括我们填满中心方块.\\n&7[Then, the final layer which is an entire square of Iron Sheetmetal, including us filling in the center Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo7.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"之后,用我们的&6锤子&f&r&a右击&f第二层的中间&7&a铁板&f金属块&f&r来创建我们的&e&l筒仓&f&r!\\n&7[After that, Right Click the Middle Iron Sheetmetal on the second layer with our Hammer to create our lSilo!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_silo.png width:100 height:125 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5DE3F2A96715BA2E.title: "&l&e筒仓&7[lSilo]&f"
	quest.5E228ACA1B13AD04.quest_desc: ["现在它能射击和猛击了!\\n&7[Now it shoots and smacks!]&f"]
	quest.5EE1DF1C8F0C1FF9.quest_desc: [
		"建造好&l&5闪电线圈&r后,我们可以让&a闪电&f击中&8&a钢栅栏&f&r,然后闪电会转化为其自身&c能量&r储备中的&c能量&r.\\n\\n&8&a钢栅栏&f&r越多,&a闪电&f击中的几率就越高!\\n\\n我在想我们是否可以使用其他模组来召唤闪电？\\n&7[After building the lLightning Coil we can have Lightning Strike the Steel Fences, which will then become Energy in its own Energy resevior. \\n\\nThe more Steel Fences the higher chance of Lightning! \\n\\nI wonder if we can use other Mods to summon Lightning?]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"为了利用大自然最具破坏性的力量,我们需要从一个&5高压线圈方块&r开始.然后,将&5&a高压蓄电池&f&r放置在&5高压线圈方块&r的相邻位置.在角落放置&8&a钢脚手架&f&r.\\n&7[To harness the power of Mother Nature's most devastating we'll need to start with a High-Voltage Coil Block. Then, place HV Accumulators adjacent to the High-Voltage Coil Block. On the corners place down Steel Scaffolding.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_lightning1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"对于下一层,在前一个方块上方放置另一个&5高压线圈方块&r.在其相邻位置,将是&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.角落将只是简单的浸渍栅栏!\\n&7[For the next layer, place another High-Voltage Coil Block on top of the previous one. Adjacent to that one, will be Light Engineering Blocks. On the corners will just be simple Treated Fences!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_lightning2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"现在,我们需要在其他的上方放置第三个&5高压线圈方块&r,周围环绕着8个&6铜线圈方块&r.\\n&7[Now, we need a third High-Voltage Coil Blocks above the others, and surrounding it will be 8 Copper Coil Blocks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_lightning3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"然后,用&6锤子&f&a右击&f&a前侧&f的&e&a轻型工程块&f&r,将其转换为&5&l闪电线圈&r!\\n&7[Then, Right Click the Light Engineering Block on the Front Side with a Hammer to convert it to the lLightning Coil!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_lightning.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"我没有为这一步制作图片,但你需要在&5&l闪电线圈&r顶部放置&8&a钢栅栏&f&r,以便让闪电击中它!\\n&7[I didn't make a picture for this step but you will need Steel Fences on top of the lLightning Coil in order to get Lightning to hit it!]&f"
	]
	quest.5EE1DF1C8F0C1FF9.title: "&5&l闪电线圈&7[lLightning Coil]&f"
	quest.5F4F7637044BD4F1.quest_desc: [
		"&2&l发酵罐&r会存放你的食物&e物品&r,过一段时间后会将它们转化为乙醇.\\n\\n有一个物品列表,你可以在&6工程师手册&r中找到,列出了可以通过背部和左侧的端口放入&2&l发酵罐&r的&e物品&r.\\n\\n如果你使用&6&a蜂蜜瓶&f&r,你可以从&a右侧&f的端口&6提取&r瓶子.\\n\\n&2&l发酵罐&r需要&c能量&r,这些能量将来自&2&l发酵罐&r顶部的端口!\\n&7[The lFermenter will hold your Food Items and after awhile will form them into Ethanol. \\n\\nThere is a list of Items, you can find it in the Engineer's Manual, of Items that can be put into the lFermenter by the Ports in the Back and Left side. \\n\\nIf you use Honey Bottles, you can Extract the Bottles out from the Port on the Right Side. \\n\\nThe lFermenter will need Energy which will come from a Port on Top of the lFermenter! ]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"一个相当简单的开始,用&8&a钢脚手架&f&r摆出一个反向的”n”形,并在其中放置&b&a流体传输管道&f&r,然后在角落放置一个&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.\\n&7[Pretty simple start, make a backwards n out of Steel Scaffolding and within it place Fluid Pipes and on the corner place a Light Engineering Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_fermenter1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"在&e&a轻型工程块&f&r上方再放置一个.在其右侧,跳过一个方块,然后放置一个&4&a红石工程块&f&r.在&e&a轻型工程块&f&r的左侧,我们将放置一个2x2的炼药锅.\\n&7[Above the Light Engineering Block place another. To the right of it, skip a Block, then place a Redstone Engineering Block. To the left of the Light Engineering Block we'll place a 2x2 of Cauldrons.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_fermenter2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"另一个简单的步骤,只需在所有炼药锅上方放置&7&a铁板&f金属&r!\\n&7[Another simple step, just place Iron Sheetmetal above all the Cauldrons!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_fermenter3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"用&6锤子&f&r&a右击&f位于&e&a轻型工程块&f&r和&4&a红石工程块&f&r之间的炼药锅.\\n&7[Right Click the Cauldron between the Light Engineering Block and Redstone Engineering Block with a Hammer.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_fermenter.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5F4F7637044BD4F1.title: "&l&2发酵机&7[lFermenter]&f"
	quest.607D9B53C632DEDE.quest_desc: ["&b&a管道阀门&f&r有助于分类和阻止&b流体&f&r流动!\\n\\n当与&b&a流体传输管道&f&r一起使用时,它们将使&b流体&f&r仅沿着&b&a管道阀门&f&r上箭头指示的方向流动.\\n\\n你也可以向其发送&4&a红石信号&f&r,使其完全停止&b流体&f&r流动!\\n&7[Pipe Valves work at helping sort and stop Fluid flow! \\n\\nWhen used with Fluid Pipes, they will make it so the Fluid only goes in direction with the arrows on the Pipe Valve. \\n\\nYou can also send it a Redstone Signal to which it will completely stop Fluid flow!]&f"]
	quest.607D9B53C632DEDE.title: "&b&a管道阀门&f&7[Pipe Valve]&f"
	quest.6140EAA6E042EF7C.quest_desc: ["&6&l天钩&r既可以作为工具,也可以作为武器.\\n\\n你可以像用剑一样用它击打生物,或者用它在你基地周围移动!\\n\\n当你靠近一根&c导线&r(&6低压&r、&e中压&r、&5高压&r、绝缘、麻绳、&8钢&r、&4红石&r)时,你可以按住&a右击&f来附着上去.然后,你可以移动来沿着&c导线&r滑行!\\n\\n如果你想在通电的&c导线&r上使用它,你需要一些升级!例如:&a高扭矩马达&f、&a绝缘把手&f和&a重击钩子&f.\\n\\n它可以容纳2个升级.\\n&7[The lSkyhook works both as a Tool and Weapon. \\n\\nYou can just smack Mobs with it as if it were a Sword or you can use it for moving around you base! \\n\\nWhen you get close to a Wire (LV, MV, HV, Insulated, Hemp, Steel, Redstone) you can Hold Right Click to attach to them. Then, you can move around to slide down the Wires! \\n\\nIf you want to use it on active Wires, you'll need some Upgrades! Upgrades like: High Torque Motor, Insulated Grip, and Heavy Impact Hooks. \\n\\nIt can hold 2 Upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.6140EAA6E042EF7C.quest_subtitle: "布克,接住!&7[Booker catch!]&f"
	quest.6140EAA6E042EF7C.title: "&6&l工程师天钩&7[lEngineer's Skyhook]&f"
	quest.63F5314A1072FA05.quest_desc: [
		"&e&l锯木机&r的工作原理与&7&l&a金属冲压机&f&r类似,使用&e&a传送带&f&r并需要额外物品.\\n\\n它分两个阶段工作,首先剥离原木.如果内部没有锯片,它将只剥离原木.第二阶段是将原木切割成木板,这需要一个锯片.\\n\\n锯片需要用大量&8钢&r合成.它们有耐久度,要插入它们,请&a右击&f锯木机后部附近的插槽.如果你想取出它们,请用&4红石&r关闭锯木机,然后在插入的位置按住Shift并&a右击&f.\\n\\n你需要在其后部顶面提供&c能量&r,并且可以通过&e&a传送带&f&r&9输入&e物品&r.&e物品&r将通过相同的&e传送带&r&6输出&r,但木屑会从&e&l机器&r前面的一个端口出来.\\n&7[The lSawmill works similar to the lMetal Press, using Conveyor Belts and needing extra Items. \\n\\nIt works in 2 stages, first it Strips the Logs. If it doesn't have a Sawblade within it, it will only Strip Logs. Second stage is cutting the Log into Planks, this needs a Sawblade. \\n\\nSawblades are Crafted with a ton of Steel. They have Durability and to insert them, Right Click the Slots near the Back of the Sawmill. If you wish to take them out, turn off the Sawmill with Redstone, then Shift Right Click where you inserted them. \\n\\nYou'll need to give it Energy on the Top of the Back Side, and you can Input Items via the Conveyor Belts. The Items will Output with those same Belts, but the Sawdust comes out of a Port in Front of the lMachine.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"用&8&a钢脚手架&f&r(别忘了&7&a重型工程块&f&r)摆出一个”I”形,并用&e&a轻型工程块&f&r填充一部分,另一部分用&7&a铁板&f金属&r填充.\\n&7[Make an I shape with Steel Scaffolding (don't forget the Heavy Engineering Block) and fill in one part with Light Engineering Blocks and the other with Iron Sheetmetal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_saw1.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"在它们下方的方块上再放置3个&e&a轻型工程块&f&r.在最左边的&7&a铁板&f金属&r上添加1个&7&a铁板&f金属&r,并在其旁边放置一个&4&a红石工程块&f&r.在顶部的&7&a铁板&f金属&r旁边,我们需要另一个&7&a重型工程块&f&r.别忘了添加&a传送带&f,这些是建造它所需要的!\\n&7[Place 3 more Light Engineering Blocks on their lower comrades. Add 1 Iron Sheetmetal on the Left most Iron Sheetmetal and next to it place a Redstone Engineering Block. Next to top Iron Sheetmetal we'll need another Heavy Engineering Block. Don't forget to add the Conveyor Belts, these are needed to Build it!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_saw2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"用我们的锤子&a右击&f中间的&7&a铁板&f金属&r!\\n&7[Right Click the middle Iron Sheetmetal with our Hammer!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_saw.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.63F5314A1072FA05.title: "&e&l锯木机&7[lSawmill]&f"
	quest.662DD269B027B6C8.quest_desc: ["你无法无线给你的&c&l&a蓄电池背包&f&r充电……但你可以&c有线&r充电!\\n\\n只需将你的充电天线连接到你的&c&l&a蓄电池背包&f&r,然后走到任何传输&c能量&r的&c导线&r旁,部分能量就会进入你的&c&l背包&r.\\n&7[You can't wirelessly charge your lAccumulator Backpack... but you can charge it wired! \\n\\nSimply attach your Charging Antenna to your lAccumulator Backpack and walk up to any Wires transporting Energy and some of it will come to your lBackpack.]&f"]
	quest.67940C0774E73217.quest_desc: ["&e物品路由器&r将&9输入&e物品&r,并根据其UI中设置的过滤规则将它们&6输出&r到特定位置!\\n\\n这些可以设置为&e传送带&r、板条箱或其他容器.\\n&7[Item Router will Input Items and Output them to certain locations based on the Filtering set in its UI! \\n\\nThese can be set to Belts, Crates, or other Inventories.]&f"]
	quest.67940C0774E73217.title: "&e物品路由器&7[Item Router]&f"
	quest.679E80EBB9A2AE7E.quest_desc: ["&b&a流体路由器&f&r对通过的&b流体&r进行分类和过滤.\\n\\n你需要在它的UI中设置配置,以确定过滤器和输出方向.一旦设置好,它会将所有输入的&b流体&r发送到预设的目的地!\\n&7[Fluid Routers sort and filter Fluids passing through. \\n\\nYou'll need to set configs within its UI to set the Filters and which Side. Once you do that, it will take all Fluids coming in and send them to where they are set to go!]&f"]
	quest.679E80EBB9A2AE7E.title: "&b&a流体路由器&f&7[Fluid Router]&f"
	quest.67FB03BE6685AFE1.quest_desc: ["要发动战争,我们首先需要宣战!\\n\\n开个玩笑,我们直接开火!这里没有外交废话!\\n\\n首先,用&d&l左轮手枪&r射击一个掠夺者.\\n\\n这将开始生成新的、更强大的掠夺者!\\n&7[To start a war we need to first declare it! \\n\\nJust kidding, we just go straight to shooting! No diplomatic crap around here! \\n\\nTo start, shoot a Pillager with a lRevolver. \\n\\nThis will start the spawning of new and harder Pillagers!]&f"]
	quest.67FB03BE6685AFE1.title: "进攻与防御&7[Offense and Defense]&f"
	quest.6B2BD6F939136F50.quest_desc: ["转盘非常简单.带有&7灰色&r方块的顶面是活动部分.\\n\\n其他面是&4&a红石接口&f&r,你将在此提供&4&a红石信号&f&r来激活它.\\n\\n激活后,它会旋转附着在顶部的任何方块.\\n\\n你可能需要用你的&6工程师锤&r敲击它来改变旋转方式!\\n&7[Turntable is pretty simple. The Top face with the Grey square will be the moving part. \\n\\nThe other faces are the Redstone Ports, where you will give a Redstone Signal to activate it. \\n\\nWhen activated it will rotate whatever Block is attached to the Top. \\n\\nYou might need to use your Engineer's Hammer on it to change how it rotates!]&f"]
	quest.6BD348735C27BB44.quest_desc: [
		"&b&l&a灌装机&f&r会灌满&e传送带&r上传来的任何&e物品&r.\\n\\n使用后面的端口向&b&l机器&r中注入&b流体&r,当储罐充满该&b流体&r时,你就知道它在工作了!\\n\\n然后,当一个&b桶&r、&b储罐&r或任何&b流体存储&r沿着&e传送带&r过来时,它将被灌满该&b流体&r.\\n\\n接着,装满&b流体&r的&b桶&r、&b储罐&r或其他容器将沿着&e传送带&r继续移动!\\n\\n顺便说一下,就像生活中的一切一样,&b&l&a灌装机&f&r需要在其后部顶面的端口中提供&c能量&r!\\n&7[The lBottling Machine will fill up whatever Item comes by on the Belt. \\n\\nUse the Ports in the Back to fill the lMachine with Fluids, you'll know it is working when the Tank is full of that Fluid! \\n\\nThen, when a Bucket, Tank, or any Fluid Storage comes down the Belt, it will be filled with that Fluid. \\n\\nThe Bucket, Tank, or whatever will then move down the Belts full of that Fluid! \\n\\nBy the way, like everything in life, the lBottling Machine will need Energy in the Ports at the Top of the Back side!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"首先,用&8&a钢脚手架&f&r摆出一个三角形.然后用&7&a铁板&f金属&r、&4&a红石工程块&f&r和一个&e&a轻型工程块&f&r填充空隙.\\n&7[To start, make a triangle out of Steel Scaffolding. Then fill the holes with Iron Sheetmetal, Redstone Engineering Block, and a Light Engineering Block.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_bottler1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"现在我们只需在前侧横着添加一个&e&a传送带&f&r.然后,在另一边添加第二个&7&a铁板&f金属&r,旁边放一个&b&a液泵&f&r,并在前一个方块上放一个&e&a轻型工程块&f&r!\\n&7[Now we just add a Conveyor Belt across the front side. Then, add a second Iron Sheetmetal on the other, a Fluid Pump next to it, and a Light Engineering Block on the previous one!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_bottler2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"只需用&6锤子&f&r敲击中间的&e&a传送带&f&r,然后砰的一声就完成了!\\n&7[Simply Hammer the middle Conveyor Belt and BOOM done!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/immersive/immersive_bottler.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6BD348735C27BB44.title: "&b&l&a灌装机&f&7[lBottling Machine]&f"
	quest.6D42D0102D1CBC19.quest_desc: ["&a附加螺旋钻&f是锋利度……但仅适用于&4&l钻头&r!\\n\\n哦对了,你一次可以拥有3个,以获得叠加的力量.\\n&7[The Additional Augers are Sharpness... just for the lDrill though! \\n\\nOh yeah and you can have 3 at a time, for stacked power.]&f"]
	quest.6F3C82072672FD17.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods 团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r为AllTheMods整合包创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下发布,未经&6AllTheMods 团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods 团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.7060290E107D92AB.quest_desc: ["很多东西都需要&c能量&r,包括一些无法放置的&e物品&r,比如&5&l磁轨炮&r!那么我们如何给它们充电呢？\\n\\n&a充电&f &a站&f就是为此而生的!\\n\\n只需从后面或底部&6输入&c能量&r,它就可以为放入其中的任何&e物品&r充电!\\n\\n这包括&5&l磁轨炮&r、&c蓄电池&r以及其他模组的物品!不过它不能给附近的方块充电……\\n&7[A lot of things will need Energy, including some Items that can't be placed down, like the lRailgun! So how do we charge them? \\n\\nThe Charging Station is our man for that job! \\n\\nSimply Input Energy from either the Back or Bottom, and it will be ready to charge any Item put within it! \\n\\nThis includes lRailguns, Accumulators, and stuff from other Mods! It can't charge Blocks near it though...]&f"]
	quest.72CE46D28C9E7452.quest_desc: ["&a瞄准镜&f可以用于&5&l磁轨炮&r和&d&l左轮手枪&r.\\n\\n使用&d&l左轮手枪&r和&5&l磁轨炮&r时,你可以按下中键使用瞄准镜,然后滚动滚轮来调整放大倍数.\\n&7[The Precision Scope can be used on both the lRailgun and the lRevolver. \\n\\nWith the lRevolver and lRailgun you can press down Middle Click to use the Scope, then you can Scroll to adjust the magnification.]&f"]
	quest.73110103EF23BFDF.quest_desc: ["&6铜&r和&7锌&r的合金.\\n\\n在&8&l沉浸工程&f&r中用途不大……我想你可以用它做告示牌……\\n&7[A mix of Copper and Zinc. \\n\\nNot really used for much in lIE... You can make Signs with it I guess...]&f"]
	quest.73110103EF23BFDF.title: "&6&a黄铜锭&f&7[Brass Ingot]&f"
	quest.763AE58CF620695E.quest_desc: ["这张&9蓝图&r,像许多其他蓝图一样,可以合成.\\n\\n&8&l&d沉浸工程&f&r自带其专属的&a旗帜图案&f!\\n\\n不过你需要&9蓝图&r来合成它们.\\n&7[This Blueprint, like many others, can be Crafted. \\n\\nlImmersive Engineering comes with it's own Banner Patterns! \\n\\nYou'll need Blueprints to craft them though.]&f"]
	quest.763AE58CF620695E.title: "&9&a旗帜图案&f蓝图&7[Banner Patterns Blueprints ]&f"
	quest.767E4FC03B6F6534.quest_desc: ["&a殷钢锭&f由&7铁&r和&7镍&r制成.\\n\\n像许多这类合金一样,它们在&8&l沉浸工程&f&r中没什么用.\\n&7[Invar Ingots are made with Iron and Nickel. \\n\\nLike a lot of these Alloys they aren't useful in lIE.]&f"]
	quest.767E4FC03B6F6534.title: "&7&a殷钢锭&f&7[Invar Ingot]&f"
	quest.7744BEC5CD328262.quest_desc: ["为了在&b水下&r挖掘方块,你需要这个升级.\\n\\n它还会给你&a水亲和模块&f!(这意味着在&b水&r中不会减慢你的挖掘速度.)\\n&7[In order to mine Blocks underwater you'll need this Upgrade. \\n\\nIt also gives you Aqua Affinity! (That means being in Water doesn't slow down your Mining.)]&f"]
	quest.78DA970F97002975.quest_desc: ["桶是储存&b流体&r的简单方式.\\n\\n有&a木桶&f和&a金属桶&f.木桶只能容纳冷流体和室温流体,不能容纳热流体或气体.而&a金属桶&f可以容纳所有类型的&b流体&r和气体.\\n\\n两种桶都可以容纳12桶&b流体&r.它们自动从&a顶面&f&9输入&r并从底面&6输出&r,但这可以更改.\\n&7[Barrels are simple ways of holding Fluids. \\n\\nThere's Wooden Barrels and Metal Barrels. Wooden ones can only hold cold and room temperature Fluids, not warm Fluids or Gases. While Metal Barrels can hold all types of Fluids and Gases. \\n\\nBoth Barrels can hold 12 Buckets of Fluid. They automatically Input from the Top side and Output to the Bottom but this can be changed.]&f"]
	quest.78DA970F97002975.title: "储存&b流体&r&7[Storing Fluids]&f"
	quest.79BEECD4E545793F.quest_desc: ["&a刀片刺网&f像蜘蛛网一样……只是更锋利!\\n\\n&a刀片刺网&f会&a伤害&f并减慢任何试图穿过它的东西,包括我们自己!\\n\\n我们可以用&6工程师剪线钳&r安全地拆除它.\\n\\n或者我们可以使用&6低压&r &c导线&r让它造成更多&a伤害&f并附加眩晕效果!\\n&7[Razor Wire works like Cobwebs... just sharper! \\n\\nThe Razor Wire will Damage and Slow anything that tries to go through it, including us! \\n\\nWe can safely take it apart with our Engineer's Wirecutters. \\n\\nOr we can use LV Wires to make it do more Damage and a Stun Effect!]&f"]
	quest.7A1E3E7E2DF17AD2.quest_desc: ["第一,是&8锯片&r.用于砍伐&2树木&r.它会砍掉被砍伐原木上方的整棵&2树&r的所有原木和树叶.\\n\\n第二,是&8&a凿岩机刀片&f&r.这个不能破坏&2树木&r,而是用作带有&a精准采集&f的&a镐子&f.它会破坏石头并给你石头而不是圆石.\\n\\n第三是&8磨削盘&r.它不会破坏&2树木&r或石头,而是会破坏&7金属方块&r!适用于&8&a钢脚手架&f&r和刮除&6铜&r的氧化层!\\n&7[First, is the Sawblade. This is used for cutting down Trees. It will chop every Log and Leaf in the Tree above the Log that is cut. \\n\\nSecond, is the Rockcutter Blade. This one can not break Trees, rather it is used as a Pickaxe with Silk Touch. It will break Stone and give you Stone instead of Cobble. \\n\\nThird is the Grinding Disk. It won't break Trees or Stone rather it'll break Metal Blocks! Good for Steel Scaffolding and scraping Oxidization off Copper!]&f"]
	quest.7A1E3E7E2DF17AD2.title: "&2&l电锯&r的弹药&7[Ammo for lBuzzsaw]&f"
	quest.7A41038180C06B00.quest_desc: ["&c连接器&r的作用是……嗯,连接!它们将&c导线&r从机器连接到&c蓄电池&r,连接到发电机,几乎连接到所有东西!\\n\\n一个&c连接器&r是&9输入&r还是&6输出&r,取决于它所连接设备的配置!\\n\\n它们也有自己的内部&c能量&r存储,电压等级决定了存储量.\\n&7[Connectors are what... well connect! They connect Wires from Machines, to Accumulators, to Generators, from pretty much everything! \\n\\nWhether a Connector Inputs or Outputs is determined by the configuration of what it is attached to! \\n\\nThey also have their own internal Energy storage, the Tier of Voltage determines how much.]&f"]
	quest.7A41038180C06B00.title: "&c连接器&7[Connectors]&f"
	quest.7AE85F4FF4DDF4F2.quest_desc: ["&a风车&f是我们可以与&a动能发电机&f一起使用的另一个选项!\\n\\n这些会自动开始转动,其速度会产生能量,所以速度越快,能量越多.\\n\\n我们如何获得速度？首先,它前面需要空间才能工作.它前面的方块越少,它转得越快!\\n\\n影响速度的另一个因素是&a改良风车叶片&f.你可以通过手持叶片&a右击&f中间的风车方块,总共添加8个&a改良风车叶片&f.\\n&7[The Windmill is another option we can use with the Kinetic Dynamo! \\n\\nThese will automatically start moving and with its speed we get Energy, so more speed more Energy. \\n\\nHow do we get speed? Well for one, it needs space in front of it to work. The less blocks in front of it, the quicker it goes! \\n\\nAnother factor into speed is Windmill Sails. You can add 8 Windmill Sails in total by Right Clicking the middle Windmill Block with the Sails in hand.]&f"]
	quest.7B447E986493AD6B.quest_desc: ["&7&a杂酚油&f&r是&l&a焦炉&f&r的副产品.\\n\\n它的主要用途是制造&a防腐木&f,这是&8&l沉浸工程&f&r中一种重要的建筑&a方块&f.\\n\\n你以后还需要它来制作另一种流体,我们到时候再操心.\\n&7[Creosote Oil is a byproduct of the lCoke Oven. \\n\\nIts main use will be for making Treated Wood, an essential Building Block of lIE. \\n\\nYou will also need it for a different Fluid later, we'll worry about it when we get there.]&f"]
	quest.7B447E986493AD6B.title: "&7&a杂酚油&f&7[Creosote Oil]&f"
	quest.7B9672C4FCFFB887.quest_desc: ["这些&9蓝图&r可以合成,而且非常便宜!\\n\\n&a警告标志&f是我们可以用&7&a金属板材&f&r、染料和这张&9蓝图&r制作的非常简单的装饰品.\\n&7[These Blueprints can be Crafted and boy are they cheap! \\n\\nWarning Signs are very simple decorations we can make with Metal Plates, Dyes, and this Blueprint.]&f"]
	quest.7B9672C4FCFFB887.title: "&9&a警告标志&f蓝图&7[Warning Signs Blueprints ]&f"
	quest.7FE273141D3DFFFD.quest_desc: ["&a燧发枪手&f是新的掠夺者的中等单位!\\n\\n他们有12颗心,没有护甲.\\n\\n他们选择的武器是一把&5&l磁轨炮&r,由他们穿戴的&a蓄电池背包&f充电!\\n\\n死亡时他们会掉落&a绿宝石&r和&7&a铁棒&f&r.\\n&7[The Fusilier is the medium unit of the new Pillagers! \\n\\nThey have 12 Hearts and no Armor. \\n\\nTheir weapon of choice is a lRailgun that is charged by their Accumulator Backpack they wear! \\n\\nOn death they will drop Emeralds and Iron Rods.]&f"]
	quest.7FE273141D3DFFFD.title: "燧发枪手&7[Fusilier]&f"
	task.02B26D0D73E5E361.title: "传送带&7[Belts]&f"
	task.0837FA64B9C50048.title: "圆锯弹药&7[Ammo for Buzzsaw]&f"
	task.0B62C759781950A1.title: "IE磁轨炮弹药&7[IE Railgun Ammo]&f"
	task.0CD67A3D64E9B49B.title: "装饰导线&7[Decor Wires]&f"
	task.0D7C60D7BFBD8CF0.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.15795AB2872E2DEE.title: "滑槽&7[Chutes]&f"
	task.173B725A839DEEAA.title: "&a普通子弹&f&7[Common Projectiles]&f"
	task.20D0DB49AFA7976F.title: "任何蓄电器&7[Any Accumulator]&f"
	task.4025792887CB9BE2.title: "导线线圈&7[Wire Coils]&f"
	task.43FDC45CF464047E.title: "温暖物品&7[Warm Items]&f"
	task.440F173D6B5EE74E.title: "继电器&7[Relays]&f"
	task.529FFD7D692AEFA5.title: "&a特种子弹&f&7[Specialized Projectiles]&f"
	task.53AF5EFD070E8761.title: "变压器&7[Transformers]&f"
	task.5580FF146C9E7EA0.title: "桶&7[Barrels]&f"
	task.56D7513E9D02F900.title: "&a钻头&f&7[Drill Heads]&f"
	task.59DC19A11848EFE1.title: "连接器&7[Connectors]&f"
	task.5CEB2D56A9EA74D0.title: "寒冷物品&7[Cold Items]&f"
	task.603A16080675C348.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.79F67E07C28F8E97.title: "Minecraft磁轨炮弹药&7[Minecraft Railgun Ammo]&f"
	task.7FED013A7F667CC6.title: "箱子&7[Crates]&f"
	quest.06094615950AC062.title: "其他传送带升级&7[Other Conveyor Upgrades]&f"
	quest.06F84E2C484FAC5B.quest_desc: ["听说过圆石生成器吗？&a造石加工机&f的工作原理类似,但将其提升到了一个新的水平.你可以让它将石头粉碎成沙砾、沙子、硅,你可以让它将其烧制成石头,你可以用它制作黑曜石,以及JEI为此机器显示的任何其他配方.\\n&7[Ever heard of a cobblestone generator? The Material StoneWork Factory works like one, but takes it to the next level. You can get it to crush stone into gravel, sand, silicon, you can get it to smelt it into stone, you can make Obsidian with it, and whatever else JEI shows for this machine.]&f"]
	quest.0B35172E47705205.quest_desc: ["是的,&b&d工业先锋&f&r也有矿石处理.这个机器使用&6&a肉汤&f&r将矿石转化为&a生矿物肉汤&f.我不是矿石医生,所以我无法用这个&a生矿物肉汤&f做任何事情.也许把它交给&a发酵站&f？\\n&7[Yes, Industrial Foregoing has ore processing too. This one uses Liquid Meat to convert an ore into Raw Ore Meat. I'm not an ore doctor, so I can't exactly do anything with this Raw Ore Meat. Maybe give it to the Fermentation Station?]&f"]
	quest.0B35172E47705205.quest_subtitle: "矿石处理:步骤 1&7[Ore Processing: Step 1]&f"
	quest.0BCCDE24D378F260.quest_subtitle: "等级:&d3&7[Tier: 3]&f"
	quest.0BCCDE24D378F260.title: "&d&a进阶机械框架&f&7[Advanced Machine Frame]&f"
	quest.0D2DD9AA960843A3.quest_desc: ["&a生物探测器&f将检测其工作区域内的实体,并在其后输出一个红石信号,信号强度等于工作区域内的实体数量.\\n\\n此机器支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[The Mob Detector will detect entities in its working area, and output a redstone signal behind it with strength equal to the amount of entities in the working area.\\n\\nThis machine supports Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.0E8647B8EB4AAC41.quest_desc: ["&a被动型生物&f -> 更多 &#FF69B4&a粉红史莱姆&f&r\\n&a敌对性生物&f -> 更多 &6肉&r\\n&7[Passive Mobs -> More &#FF69B4Pink Slime\\nHostile Mobs -> More Meat]&f"]
	quest.0E8647B8EB4AAC41.title: "&a粉红史莱姆&f \\ &a肉汤&f&7[Pink Slime \\\\ Liquid Meat]&f"
	quest.0EA9E52B67B533DF.quest_desc: ["橡胶烧炼后会变成塑料,这是&d工业先锋&f中的主要资源.\\n&7[When Rubber is smelted it turns into Plastic, which is the main resource in Industrial Foregoing.]&f"]
	quest.0EC2053B191C55C6.quest_desc: ["从原木中提取乳胶,供电时运行更快.\\n\\n查看JEI了解可接受的原木和乳胶数量.最好使用的原木是金合欢木或红树木.\\n&7[Extracts Latex from logs, runs faster when given power.\\n\\nCheck JEI for acceptable logs and Latex amounts. The best log to use is Acacia or Mangrove.]&f"]
	quest.0FAAE744E156D8EF.quest_desc: ["&b&a菌丝网络产能反应堆&f&r由所有菌丝发电机同时工作组成,位于反应堆方块附近,它总共产生&a25MFE/t&r.\\n\\n听起来都不错,但你需要自动化一些东西才能让它工作,看看每个菌丝发电机工作需要消耗什么,然后将其自动化,大多数东西很简单,但其他的就没那么简单了……&o看看祛魔菌丝发电机&r.\\n\\n但是在你完成所有自动化之后,你不必只停留在一个反应堆,你可以制造更多反应堆.\\n&7[The Mycelial Reactor consists of all the Mycelial Generators working at the same time, near the reactor block, and it produces a total of 25MFE/t.\\n\\nAll sounds good, but you need to automate some stuff to get it working, see what each Mycelial Generator consumes to work, and automate it, most things are simple, but others, not that much... looking at Disenchanting Mycelial Generator.\\n\\nBut after you get it all automated, you don't need to stop at one, you can make more reactors.]&f"]
	quest.0FAAE744E156D8EF.quest_subtitle: "&a菌丝网络产能反应堆&f, huh?&7[Mycelial Reactor, huh?]&f"
	quest.15551AC6C68E12E0.quest_desc: ["基本上是&b&d工业先锋&f&r的刷怪笼.它使用&a精华&f以及一个装在&a生物捕捉工具&f中的生物来生成该生物的副本.\\n\\nBoss和其他无法放入刷怪笼*的生物同样被&a自动刷怪机&f列入黑名单.\\n\\n*&8有一些例外,在启用高级提示(F3 + H)时按住SHIFT查看刷怪蛋,看看是否能找到&a自动刷怪机&f黑名单标签.\\n&7[Basically the spawner of Industrial Foregoing. It uses Essence along with a mob in a Mob Imprisonment Tool to spawn a copy of that mob.\\n\\nBosses and other mobs that cannot be put into a spawner* are blacklisted from the Mob Duplicator as well.\\n\\n*With a few exceptions, hold SHIFT on a spawn egg while advanced tooltips (F3 + H) are enabled to see if you can find the Mob Duplicator Blacklist tag.]&f"]
	quest.1684D52FDAAC894B.quest_desc: ["还记得那个不是矿石医生的家伙吗？&a洗矿厂&f代替他处理来自&a洗矿厂&f的&a生矿物肉汤&f,将其转化为&a发酵矿物肉汤&f.这台机器有4种模式.\\n\\n1. 2倍矿石处理速率,处理时间5秒.\\n2. 3倍矿石处理速率,处理时间45秒.\\n3. 4倍矿石处理速率,处理时间120秒.使用&#FF69B4&a粉红史莱姆&f&r作为催化剂.\\n4. 5倍矿石处理速率,处理时间300秒.使用&b以太气体&r作为催化剂.\\n&7[Remember that Not-An-Ore-Doctor fella? The Washing Factory fills in for him, to handle the Raw Ore Meat from the Washing Factory, turning it into Fermented Ore Meat. This machine has 4 modes.\\n\\n1. 2x ore processing rate, 5 seconds to process.\\n2. 3x ore processing rate, 45 seconds to process.\\n3. 4x ore processing rate, 120 seconds to process. Uses &#FF69B4Pink Slime as a catalyst.\\n4. 5x ore processing rate, 300 seconds to process. Uses Ether Gas as a catalyst.]&f"]
	quest.1684D52FDAAC894B.quest_subtitle: "矿石处理:步骤 2&7[Ore Processing: Step 2]&f"
	quest.1823CC81D613892B.quest_desc: ["&a屠宰场&f &l删除&r其工作区域内的生物,并将该生物转化为&#FF69B4&a粉红史莱姆&f&r和&6&a肉汤&f&r.\\n\\n&a被动型生物&f -> 更多 &#FF69B4&a粉红史莱姆&f&r\\n&a敌对性生物&f -> 更多 &6肉&r\\n\\n此机器支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[The Mob Slaughter Factory ldeletes mobs in its working area, and converts that mob into &#FF69B4Pink Slime and Liquid Meat.\\n\\nPassive Mobs -> More &#FF69B4Pink Slime\\nHostile Mobs -> More Meat\\n\\nThis machine supports Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.1BA3D15FFE7DBE59.quest_desc: ["在&b&d工业先锋&f&r中,主要资源之一是&f乳胶&r.它用于合成&a机器框架&f,这是制造机器和升级所必需的.\\n\\n制造乳胶非常简单,&a&a流体开采&f&r从&6原木&r中提取乳胶(金合欢木和红树木产出最多).\\n\\n------------------------\\n\\n现在关于制造塑料:塑料是通过烧炼&a干橡胶&f得到的——&a干橡胶&f是在&a&a胶乳加工机&f&r中制造的,该机器将乳胶转化为&a干橡胶&f.\\n\\n&b所以基本上是 乳胶 -> &a干橡胶&f -> 塑料.\\n&7[In Industrial Foregoing, one of the main resources is Latex. Its used to craft Machine Frames, needed to make machines and upgrades.\\n\\nMaking Latex is pretty simple, Fluid Extractor extracts Latex from Logs (Acacia and Mangrove give the most).\\n\\n------------------------\\n\\nNow about making Plastic: Plastic results from smelting Dry Rubber - which is made in the Latex Processing Unit, that transforms Latex into Dry Rubber.\\n\\nSo basically Latex -> Dry Rubber -> Plastic.]&f"]
	quest.1BA3D15FFE7DBE59.quest_subtitle: "乳胶和塑料？嗯？&7[Latex and Plastic? Huh?]&f"
	quest.1BA3D15FFE7DBE59.title: "乳胶和塑料？嗯？&7[Latex and Plastic? Huh?]&f"
	quest.1F66CDC9799B5DEC.quest_desc: ["我发现大多数扳手都无法旋转&b&d工业先锋&f&r的机器,这让我很烦恼.为了解决这个问题,我整理了一份我能找到的所有能够旋转&bIF&r机器的扳手列表.这些主要是在&a镭射钻&f上测试的,所以结果将主要集中于此.有些扳手可能不适用于其他机器.\\n\\n点击此任务中的任务以查看此任务所有有效的扳手.\\n&7[I found myself annoyed at being unable to rotate Industrial Foregoing Machines with most Wrenches. To help with this, I have compiled a list of all the wrenches that I can find that are capable of rotating IF machines. These were tested primarily on the Laser Drill, so the results will focus primarily on that. Some wrenches might not work with other machines.\\n\\nClick the task in this quest to view all valid Wrenches for this quest.]&f"]
	quest.224C07AC71C5F40E.quest_desc: ["对其工作区域内的植物施加&l&a骨粉&f&r或&#8B4513肥料&r.这将持续对同一作物施加&#8B4513肥料&r,直到该作物无法再接受&l&a骨粉&f&r,然后才会转移到下一个植物.这意味着机器可能会卡在总是接受&l&a骨粉&f&r的植物上,例如&e向日葵&r,或者永远无法达到最终生长状态的植物上.\\n\\n此机器支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[Applies lBone Meal or &#8B4513Fertilizer to plants in its working area. This will continue applying &#8B4513Fertilizer to the same crop until that crop can no longer accept lBone Meal before moving on to the next plant. This means that the machine can get stuck on plants that always accept lBone Meal, such as Sunflowers, or plants that never reach their final growth state.\\n\\nThis machine supports Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.22702838FC507A2E.quest_desc: ["&a水培床&f使用能量和&9水&r来生长种植在其上的作物和树苗.它支持几乎所有你能想到的作物.你还可以提供&b以太气体&r,这样机器就会自动收获作物并将作物产物放入其内部缓冲区.这也可以为水培模拟处理器收集作物数据,以便在模拟&a水培床&f中使用.\\n\\n树苗将需要空间来生长.\\n&7[The Hydroponic Bed uses Energy and Water to grow crops and saplings planted on it. It supports pretty much any crop you can imagine. You can also provide Ether Gas so the machine automatically harvests the crop and puts the crop's results into its internal buffer. This can also gather crop data for a Hydroponic Simulation Processor, to use in a Simulated Hydroponic Bed.\\n\\nSaplings will require space to grow.]&f"]
	quest.2580135392DEF522.quest_desc: ["是否觉得标准的&a水培床&f太卡了？&m放不下足够的灵魂涌动？&r哦对了,我们这个整合包里没有灵魂涌动.让我介绍一下模拟&a水培床&f.这将使用一个水培模拟处理器和一个种子/树苗来虚拟地生长你选择的任何作物……你甚至不需要&9水&r和&b以太气体&r.除此之外,水培模拟处理器会随着种植更多作物而变得更好,尽管在模拟&a水培床&f中其缩放速度较慢.\\n\\n甚至不要费心去最大化处理器.这将花费难以想象的时间.肯定比我制作&d末影接口&f任务所需的时间要长得多.\\n&7[Ever feel like the standard Hydroponic Bed is too laggy? Can't fit enough Soul Surges? Oh right we don't have Soul Surges in this pack. Allow me to introduce the Simulated Hydroponic Bed. This will use a Hydroponic Simulation Processor and a seed/sapling to grow any crop of your choice...virtually. You don't even need Water and Ether Gas for this one. On top of this, Hydroponic Simulation Processors get better over time as they grow more crops, though the rate at which it scales is slower in a Simulated Hydroponic Bed.\\n\\nDon't even bother trying to maximize the Processor. It will take an unfathomably long time. Much longer than what it would take for me to make the quests for Ender IO, for sure.]&f"]
	quest.2580135392DEF522.quest_subtitle: "HNN但是用于作物？&7[HNN but for crops?]&f"
	quest.2580135392DEF522.title: "模拟&a水培床&f&7[Simulated Hydroponic Bed]&f"
	quest.2782EA80C1C74EBD.quest_desc: ["&a屠宰机&f &l删除&r其工作区域内的生物,收集该生物的掉落物,并将该生物本应获得的&a经验&r转化为&a精华&f.你也可以选择使用本应获得的经验来为&a屠宰机&f附加抢夺效果.\\n\\nBoss和其他无法放入刷怪笼的生物被&a屠宰机&f”列入黑名单”.它们不会被&l删除&r,而是受到75点伤害&a每次&f.\\n\\n此机器支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[The Mob Crusher ldeletes mobs in its working area, collecting that mob's loot, as well as converting the Experience that mob would get into Essence. You can also optionally use the would be Experience to apply Looting to the Mob Crusher instead.\\n\\nBosses and other mobs that cannot go into spawners are \"blacklisted\" from the Mob Crusher. Instead of being ldeleted, they take 75 damage per operation.\\n\\nThis machine supports Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.2782EA80C1C74EBD.quest_subtitle: "无尽传送门粉碎机,也是&7[Endless Gateway Crusher, too]&f"
	quest.287B47E27EBC2C18.quest_desc: ["&a自动附魔台&f基本上是一个自动化的附魔台.当提供装备/书和&a精华&f时,它会随机为该物品附魔.此机器可以直接使用其上方的储罐中的流体,以增加附魔装备和书的潜力.\\n&7[The Enchantment Factory is basically an automated Enchanting Table. When provided with Gear/Books and Essence, it will enchant that item with something random. This machine can use fluids from tanks directly above it, to allow for an increased potential for enchanting gear and books.]&f"]
	quest.28B3591BFC0FA08B.quest_desc: ["&a凋灵生成器&f,顾名思义,建造凋灵.它是&aATM之星&f的凋灵罗盘的一部分.\\n\\n&8你可能想用一些防凋灵玻璃将&a凋灵生成器&f包裹起来,以防止凋灵将其炸毁.\\n&7[The Wither Builder, as its name implies, builds Withers. It's part of the Wither's Compass for the ATM Star.\\n\\nYou may want to encase the Wither Builder in some witherproof glass, to prevent Withers from blowing it up.]&f"]
	quest.2CCFEE98FE3B2E97.quest_desc: ["这些机器用于自动化方块放置/破坏.这在自动化乳胶生产时特别有用.\\n&7[These machines are used to automate block placing/breaking. This is especially useful when automating Latex.]&f"]
	quest.2CCFEE98FE3B2E97.title: "方块&7[Blocks]&f"
	quest.2DC012EF21FB359E.quest_desc: ["&a附魔提取机&f可以自动从装备上移除附魔.你可以选择将其转移到书上,或者将附魔转化为&a精华&f.\\n&7[The Enchantment Extractor can automatically remove enchantments from gear. You can have it either go onto a Book, or have the enchantment be converted into Essence.]&f"]
	quest.2E8E292ED596A104.quest_desc: ["&a镭射聚焦透镜&f可以使矿石镭射钻更专注于某种颜色的矿石.在JEI中查看哪种透镜对特定类型的矿石效果最好.它还决定了流体镭射钻可以产生哪种流体类型.\\n&7[Laser Lens can make Ore Lasers focus more on a certain color of ore. Check in JEI to see what lens work best for a certain type of ore. It also determines what fluid type can be produced by Fluid Lasers.]&f"]
	quest.2F69010E1FA2787D.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r为在AllTheMods整合包中使用而创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下授权,未经&6AllTheMods Team&r明确许可,此任务不允许在任何非&6AllTheMods Team&r发布的公开整合包中使用.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.3027584AA6138E6D.title: "传送带插入 \\ 提取&7[Conveyor Insertion \\\\ Extraction]&f"
	quest.321FA7348E532F4E.quest_desc: ["乳胶是一种用于制造&a干橡胶&f的流体,但它也可以用于&a化学溶解室&f中的一些东西.\\n&7[Latex is a fluid used to make Dry Rubber, but it can also be used for some things in the Dissolution Chamber.]&f"]
	quest.321FA7348E532F4E.title: "乳胶&7[Latex]&f"
	quest.33532408B21A5378.quest_desc: ["&a木质燃料发电机&f使用像煤炭这样的可燃燃料产生少量FE.\\n&7[The Pitiful Generator generates a small amount of FE using burnable fuels like Coal.]&f"]
	quest.339DF320DDCAD98B.quest_desc: ["传输器可用于在相距1个方块的容器之间传输物品和/或流体.你需要在提取侧放置一个传输器,在插入侧放置另一个.要更改这些模式,&a右击&f中间区域.\\n\\n你可以在同一个方块中拥有多种传输器类型.你可以用插件升级这些传输器.速度插件增加传输速度,&a效率&f插件增加传输数量.\\n&7[Transporters can be used to transport Items and/or Fluids between inventories that are 1 block away. You need a Transporter in the extraction side and another in the insertion side. To change these modes, right click the middle area.\\n\\nYou can have multiple transporter types in the same block. You can upgrade these with Addons. Speed to increase transfer speed, Efficiency to increase transfer amount.]&f"]
	quest.339DF320DDCAD98B.title: "物品 \\ &a流体传输&f&7[Item \\\\ Fluid Transport]&f"
	quest.34AA079FFAFC64BD.quest_desc: ["&b&d工业先锋&f&r矿石处理系列的最终步骤,&a流体筛分机&f.这将使用沙子过滤掉&a发酵矿物肉汤&f的有用部分,给我们一些粉末.用那些粉末做任何你想做的事.烧炼它,将其混合成合金.\\n&7[The final step of the ore processing lineup of Industrial Foregoing, the Fluid Sieving Machine. This will use sand to filter out the useful part of Fermented Ore Meat, giving us some dust. Do whatever you want with that dust. Smelt it, mix it into an alloy.]&f"]
	quest.34AA079FFAFC64BD.quest_subtitle: "矿石处理:步骤 3&7[Ore Processing: Step 3]&f"
	quest.3514E9C1A8C7400C.quest_subtitle: "等级:&b2&7[Tier: 2]&f"
	quest.3514E9C1A8C7400C.title: "&b简易&a机器框架&f&7[Simple Machine Frame]&f"
	quest.3AFDE3396861A944.quest_desc: ["&a自动型铁砧&f是一个自动化的铁砧.它可以自动将&a附魔书&f应用到装备上.使用&a精华&f代替&a经验&r.此机器可以直接使用其上方的储罐中的流体,以增加附魔装备的潜力.\\n&7[The Enchantment Applicator is an automated Anvil. It can apply Enchanted Books to gear automatically. Uses Essence in place of Experience. This machine can use fluids from tanks directly above it, to allow for an increased potential for enchanting gear.]&f"]
	quest.3CB7884B7B32CF00.quest_desc: ["获取你的第一份&b以太气体&r可能有点吓人.\\n\\n&b以太气体&r是通过钻取凋灵制造的,使用带有&5&a紫色透镜&f&r的&a流体钻&f.\\n\\n但不用担心凋灵,&d工业先锋&f有一台机器专门帮助你完成这项任务.&4&a冷凝室&f&r是一台机器,可以冻结其上方3x3区域内的任何东西,包括凋灵.\\n\\n&c希望你不要耗尽电力,因为如果你耗尽了……我希望你准备好与&0凋灵&c战斗.因此,我建议使用某种防凋灵玻璃,例如来自Mob Grinding Utils的&a遮光玻璃&f,或者启用强化模式的Crystalix玻璃.&c\\n&7[Getting your first Ether Gas might be a little bit scary.\\n\\nEther Gas is made from drilling a Wither, using a Fluid Drill with a Purple Lens.\\n\\nBut don't worry about the Wither, Industrial Foregoing has a machine just to help you with that task. The Stasis Chamber is a machine that freezes in place anything that is on top of it in a 3x3 area, including the Wither.\\n\\nHope you don't run out of power, because if you do... I hope you're ready to fight the Wither. Because of this, I recommend using some kind of Wither-Proof Glass, such as Tinted Glass from Mob Grinding Utils, or Crystalix Glass with Reinforced Mode enabled.]&f"]
	quest.3CB7884B7B32CF00.quest_subtitle: "以太气体？嗯？&7[Ether Gas? Huh?]&f"
	quest.3E6706BC4C318A40.quest_desc: ["污水处理器从其工作区域内的动物身上制造&#8B4513污水&r,并吸收玩家的&a经验&r转化为&a精华&f.\\n\\n&a污水堆肥机&f可以将&#8B4513污水&r转化为&#8B4513肥料&r.\\n\\n污水处理器支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[The Sewer makes &#8B4513Sewage from animals in its working area, as well as absorb Experience from players to convert into Essence.\\n\\nThe Sewage Composter can turn &#8B4513Sewage into &#8B4513Fertilizer.\\n\\nThe Sewer supports Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.3E6706BC4C318A40.quest_subtitle: "刚从粪田新鲜出炉,你的恐怖感&7[Fresh from the Manure Field, your spookiness]&f"
	quest.3E6706BC4C318A40.title: "污水处理器&7[Sewer]&f"
	quest.408203C29BAABA44.quest_desc: ["仅用于一件事.\\n&7[Only used for one thing.]&f"]
	quest.418E57E34FFC19E1.quest_desc: ["&a镭射钻基座&f是&b&d工业先锋&f&r的&a虚空矿工&f,能够凭空变出矿石.透镜允许你偏爱特定颜色的矿石,例如蓝色对应青金石.\\n\\n&a流体镭射钻基座&f从稀薄的空气中或从特定生物身上产生流体.这些需要你使用特定的透镜.用于产生流体的生物会受到伤害,因此建议使用&a冷凝室&f来处理.\\n\\n&a镭射钻&f为其工作区域内的&a镭射钻基座&f提供进度.\\n&7[The Ore Laser Base is Industrial Foregoing's Void Miner, being able to conjure ores out of thin air. Lens allow you to favor a specific color of ore, such as Blue for Lapis.\\n\\nThe Fluid Laser Base produces Fluids out of either thin air or from specific mobs. These require you to use specific Lens. Mobs that are used to produce Fluids will take damage, so using a Stasis Chamber for it is recommended.\\n\\nLaser Drills provide progress to the Laser Base in its working area.]&f"]
	quest.418E57E34FFC19E1.quest_subtitle: "&a虚空矿工&f&7[Void Miner]&f"
	quest.418E57E34FFC19E1.title: "&a镭射钻&f&7[Laser Drill]&f"
	quest.41E8550FC36ABCA5.quest_desc: ["无限工具,之所以这么叫是因为它们能够近乎无限地充电.提高工具的等级可以赋予所述工具特殊的能力.在其中装有&5生物燃料&r会使它们更高效,在使用时消耗燃料而不是能量.\\n\\n有7个等级:\\n粗糙\\n普通\\n罕见\\n稀有\\n史诗\\n传说\\n神器\\n\\n要了解更多关于每个无限工具的信息,请查看&d工业先锋&f的手册(这样我就不必在一个任务中涵盖这么多无限工具了)!\\n&7[Infinity Tools, so called because of their ability to be charged near-infinitely. Increasing the tier of the tool can give said tool special perks. Having Biofuel in them will make them more efficient, by consuming the fuel instead of power when used.\\n\\nThere are 7 tiers:\\nPoor\\nCommon\\nUncommon\\nRare\\nEpic\\nLegendary\\nArtifact\\n\\nTo learn more about each Infinity Tool, check out Industrial Foregoing's Manual (so that I don't have to cover so many infinity tools in one quest)!]&f"]
	quest.41E8550FC36ABCA5.title: "无限工具&7[Infinity Tools]&f"
	quest.427C3AFC0FF131CD.title: "流体&7[Fluids]&f"
	quest.483E93500E645835.quest_desc: ["至少比锭块用途更广.\\n&7[It's at least more versatile than the ingot.]&f"]
	quest.485AFAE5BBEF2FC7.quest_desc: ["&a动物资源收获机&f会剪&z绵羊&r的毛并给&8牛&r挤奶.\\n\\n&a饲育机&f会喂养动物,使它们能够繁殖.\\n\\n&a幼仔分管机&f会将幼崽传送到其后方.\\n\\n所有这些机器都支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[The Animal Rancher shears zSheep and milks Cows.\\n\\nThe Animal Feeder feeds animals so they can breed.\\n\\nThe Animal Baby Separator teleports babies behind it.\\n\\nAll of these machines support Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.485AFAE5BBEF2FC7.title: "动物&7[Animals]&f"
	quest.4A8C60412E59E971.quest_desc: ["这台机器可以对附魔物品和未附魔物品进行分类.&a附魔&f物品会进入顶部物品栏,而未附魔物品会进入底部物品栏.\\n&7[This machine can sort enchanted items and unenchanted items. The enchanted items end up in the top inventory, while the unenchanted items end up in the bottom inventory.]&f"]
	quest.4C366515E3CCB0B2.quest_desc: ["通过管道输送的肉,美味.\\n&7[Meat through a tube, yummy.]&f"]
	quest.4DB5DD6E20619B4D.quest_desc: ["用于提升机器性能.共有8个等级的扩展插件,另有4个专门用于范围扩展.\\n&7[Used to make machines better. There's 8 tiers of addons, and 4 more specifically for Range.]&f"]
	quest.4F3EF1574F31A7E2.quest_desc: ["&a冷凝室&f可以将其工作区域内的生物固定住.处于停滞状态下的生物也会受到冷凝室的治疗.需要更多治疗？装一些扩展插件!\\n&7[The Stasis Chamber can hold mobs in place in its working area. The mobs held under stasis are also healed by the Chamber. Need more healing? Get some addons!]&f"]
	quest.538186D01429F05F.quest_desc: [
		"在这个任务中,我们将重点学习如何使用AE2来自动化&c&a自动炼药机&f&r.首先,搭建一个如下所示的装置:\\n&7[In this quest, we will be focusing on using AE2 to automate the Potion Brewer. First, build a setup like so:]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/potionbrewerdemonstration.png width:175 height:200 align:center}"
		"(&a创造能源元件&f作为你主网络的占位符)\\n&7[(The Creative Energy Cell serves as a placeholder for your main network)]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"我们需要一个&9输出总线&r或一个&9接口&r来为&c&a自动炼药机&f&r填充&1水&r和&a&6烈焰粉&r&f.&a&6烈焰粉&r&f将用作燃料.暂时不要提供玻璃瓶,因为它们会用&a水瓶&f填满你的网络.\\n&7[We'll need either an Export Bus or an Interface to fill the Potion Brewer with Water and Blaze Powder. The Blaze Powder will be used as fuel. Do not provide bottles yet, as they will fill your network with Water Bottles.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"下一步是获取一个\\n&7[The next step will be to get an]&f"
		"&5高级样板供应器&r.查看扩展 \\ 高级AE章节以了解更多关于如何使用它的信息.接下来,我们需要编码一个样板.一个例子是酿造&4&a终极治疗药水&f&r,专注于模块化蜜蜂的皇家款待.像这样编码样板:3个&a玻璃瓶&f、1个&a地狱疣&f、1个闪烁的&a西瓜片&f,产出3个&4治疗药水&r.我们将在这里使用&5高级供应器&r的两个特殊功能.首先是它能够将物品发送到特定面.我们将使用此功能将&a玻璃瓶&f发送到机器的顶部.使用&5高级&a样板编码台&f&r来编码样板,像这样:\\n&7[Advanced Pattern Provider. Check the Extended \\\\ Advanced AE chapter to learn more about how to use it. Next, we'll need to encode a pattern. An example will be to brew a Potion of Healing, focused on Royal Treats for Modular Bees. Encode the pattern like so: 3 Glass Bottles, 1 Nether Wart, 1 Glistering Melon Slice, to produce 3 Potions of Healing. We'll be using both of the Advanced Provider's special abilities here. First is its ability to send items to a specific side. We'll be using this to send Glass Bottles to the TOP side of the machine. Use the Advanced Pattern Encoder to encode the pattern, like so:]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/advanced_pattern.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"接下来,我们需要在&5高级供应器&r上启用过滤导入.这将使&5高级供应器&r只接受与当前激活的合成任务相匹配的物品.这意味着它不会过早地接受药水.你也可以添加&a处理&f扩展插件来辅助这一点,特别是对于可能使用同一供应器的足够大的合成任务.\\n\\n最后,你需要像这样配置&a自动炼药机&f的面:\\n&7[Next, we need to enable Filtered Import on the Advanced Provider. This will make it so that the Advanced Provider only accepts items that match currently active crafting jobs. This means it won't accept potions prematurely. You can also add Processing Addons to aid with this, especially with large enough crafting jobs that may use that same provider.\\n\\nLastly, you'll have to configure the sides of the Potion Brewer like so:]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/blaze_input.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/bottle_input.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/brewing_input.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/output.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"如果你使用的是&9接口&r方法,请像这样配置面:\\n&7[If you're using the Interface method, configure the sides like so:]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/blaze_input_for_interface.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/industrialforegoing/water_for_interface.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"可选地,你可以在&5高级供应器&r和&c炼药机&r之间放置一个传输标签.\\n\\n如果你对这个设置仍然感到困惑,或者更愿意观看视频,请查看我在这里链接的视频,来自ChosenArchitect:\\n&7[Optionally, you can place a Transfer Label between the Advanced Provider and the Brewer.\\n\\nIf you're still confused by this setup, or would rather watch a video, check out the video I have linked here, from ChosenArchitect:]&f"
		"{\"clickEvent\":{\"action\":\"open_url\",\"value\":\"https://youtu.be/DOW4xkxqp6g?si=paZ2xFKyycPumqaSt=427\"},\"color\":\"blue\",\"text\":\"VIDEO LINK HERE\",\"underlined\":true} "
	]
	quest.538186D01429F05F.quest_subtitle: "使用AE2&7[Using AE2]&f"
	quest.538186D01429F05F.title: "自动化&a自动炼药机&f&7[Automating the Potion Brewer]&f"
	quest.540B857F043C24D5.quest_desc: ["&a生物反应器&f使用&9水&r和一堆不同的材料(查看JEI了解所有有效的生物反应器输入)生产&5生物燃料&r.你提供的材料种类越多,生物反应器生产&5生物燃料&r的效率就越高.\\n\\n&a生物燃油发电机&f使用&5生物反应器&r制造的&5生物燃料&r来产生FE.\\n&7[The Bioreactor produces Biofuel with Water and a bunch of different materials (check JEI for all valid Bioreactor Inputs). The more types of materials you provide, the more efficient the Bioreactor is at producing Biofuel.\\n\\nThe Biofuel Generator uses Biofuel made from the Bioreactor to generate FE.]&f"]
	quest.540B857F043C24D5.title: "生物能源&7[Bio Power]&f"
	quest.55820773BDD5319D.quest_desc: ["&b&d工业先锋&f&r(简称IF)是一个科技模组,添加了许多具有各种不同用途的机器.\\n\\n要开始使用,合成一个&a可怜的&a机器框架&f&r.\\n&7[Industrial Foregoing (IF for short) is a tech mod that adds many machines with various different uses.\\n\\nTo get started, craft a Pity Machine Frame.]&f"]
	quest.55820773BDD5319D.quest_subtitle: "等级:&a1&7[Tier: 1]&f"
	quest.55820773BDD5319D.title: "&d工业先锋&f&7[Industrial Foregoing]&f"
	quest.57C4A0BAE739E903.quest_desc: ["&a化学溶解室&f用于合成更高级的机器.\\n\\n你需要将某种流体与你要合成的物品所需的材料一起放入其中.查看JEI.\\n&7[The Dissolution Chamber is used to craft more advanced machines.\\n\\nYou will need to put a certain fluid in it along with the items needed for what you are crafting. Check JEI.]&f"]
	quest.57C4A0BAE739E903.quest_subtitle: "工作台？&7[The Crafting Table?]&f"
	quest.5FE631066CAB7397.quest_desc: ["用于轻松捕捉和运输生物.\\n&7[Used to trap and transport mobs easily.]&f"]
	quest.605A5AC65BC7E864.quest_desc: ["&a钓鱼机&f可以自动钓鱼.可以钓到鱼、宝藏、附魔书和一些其他东西.不过,它钓不到蜜蜂,你得手动去钓那个.\\n\\n必须放置在一个3x3的&9水&r池(或更大)上方.\\n&7[The Marine Fisher can fish automatically. Can catch fish, treasures, enchanted books, and some other stuff. Can't catch bees, though, you'll have to fish manually for that one.\\n\\nMust be placed above a 3x3 Water pool (or bigger).]&f"]
	quest.616CFD4078D67B51.quest_desc: ["传送带是另一种运输物品的方式.它们适用于物品、实体,甚至流体.它们可以通过传送带升级与世界互动.\\n\\n你可以用荧石升级传送带使其更快,或用塑料升级使其停止拾取物品.\\n&7[Conveyors are another way to transport stuff. They work with items, entities, and even fluids. They can interact with the world with Conveyor Upgrades.\\n\\nYou can upgrade conveyors with Glowstone to make them faster, and with Plastic to stop them from picking up items. ]&f"]
	quest.65C147F5282E8FCD.quest_desc: ["无限充能器是你为无限工具&a充电&f的最佳选择.它能存储&l大量&r的FE,非常适合无限工具.\\n\\n它也可以为其他东西充电.\\n&7[The Infinity Charger is your best option for charging Infinity Tools. It holds a llot of FE, perfect for the Infinity Tools.\\n\\nIt can charge other stuff, too.]&f"]
	quest.690CFF61CE787D43.quest_desc: ["塑料是&b&d工业先锋&f&r的主要资源,你现在可以使用一些非常有用的机器了!\\n&7[Plastic is the main resource of Industrial Foregoing, you now have access to some very useful machines!]&f"]
	quest.6C001E18093FC037.quest_desc: ["&a收割机&f会收获其工作区域内的植物.收获的植物可能会产生&#5919B6污泥&r,可用于&a污泥精炼机&f.当供应&b以太气体&r时,&a收割机&f会自动重新种植作物.\\n\\n&a播种机&f会自动种植作物和树苗.它有9个颜色编码的物品栏槽位,对应&a播种机&f顶部的彩色标记.机器的工作区域被分成9个部分,分别对应各个物品栏槽位.\\n\\n这两台机器都支持范围扩展插件.\\n&7[The Plant Gatherer harvests plants in its working area. Harvested plants can give &#5919B6Sludge, which can be used in a Sludge Refiner. When supplied with Ether Gas, the Plant Gatherer will automatically replant crops.\\n\\nThe Plant Sower automatically plants crops and saplings. It has 9 color coded inventory slots, which correspond to the colored markings on top of the Plant Sower. The working area of the machine is divided into 9 segments, which correspond to the various inventory slots.\\n\\nBoth of these machines support Range Addons.]&f"]
	quest.6C001E18093FC037.title: "植物&7[Plants]&f"
	quest.6E131A32A96D7BF5.quest_desc: ["&a污泥精炼机&f可以使用&#5919B6污泥&r生产诸如泥土、沙砾、&a灵魂沙&f……等等的东西……查看JEI了解其余产物.\\n&7[The Sludge Refiner can use &#5919B6Sludge to produce stuff like Dirt, Gravel, Soul Sand...whatever...check JEI for the rest.]&f"]
	quest.6FF04DD735346BED.quest_desc: ["将乳胶转化为&a干橡胶&f.使用750 mB乳胶和500 mB &9水&r生产1个&a干橡胶&f.\\n&7[Turns Latex into Dry Rubber. Uses 750 mB of Latex and 500 mB of Water to produce 1 Dry Rubber.]&f"]
	quest.7B4AF35313D7D779.quest_subtitle: "等级:&64&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.7B4AF35313D7D779.title: "&6至尊&a机器框架&f&7[Supreme Machine Frame]&f"
	quest.7CB4D47ABC295B92.quest_desc: ["它酿造药水.很像标准的酿造台,它需要&a烈焰粉&f作为燃料,并使用玻璃瓶.不过,与酿造台不同的是,它可以自动为这些玻璃瓶装水.\\n\\n与其他任务中我简要概述机器不同,我将在另一个任务中提供一个自动化这台机器的设置,因为它在某些方面相当笨拙且不直观.\\n&7[It brews potions. Much like a standard Brewing Stand, it requires Blaze Powder as fuel, and uses bottles. Unlike a Brewing Stand, though, it can autofill those bottles with water.\\n\\nUnlike with other quests where I give a brief overview of the machine, I will provide a setup in another quest to automate this machine, as it is fairly janky and unintuitive in some areas.]&f"]
	quest.7E39FB9F3E973009.quest_subtitle: "不,这不是&d通用机械&f的化学品,这是凋灵牛奶&7[No, it's not a Mekanism Chemical, it's Wither Milk]&f"
	quest.7E39FB9F3E973009.title: "以太气体&7[Ether Gas]&f"
	task.1F1A69738DE70DB6.title: "The &a菌丝网络产能反应堆&f&7[The Mycelial Reactor]&f"
	task.335D80E83360A7DB.title: "理解以太气体&7[Understanding Ether Gas]&f"
	task.38E166AC8F55D42E.title: "升级&7[Upgrades]&f"
	task.391AB5CA0E5C35FD.title: "理解乳胶与塑料&7[Understanding Latex and Plastic]&f"
	task.4031B8B8FBDDEEE4.title: "传输标签&7[Transfer Labels]&f"
	task.5BCE4EFD40BF767D.title: "适用于IF机器的扳手&7[Wrenches that work with IF Machines]&f"
	task.6B17A0D9906E8C90.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6D00B76B8A141BB8.title: "任意 #advanced_ae:adv_pattern_provider&7[Any #advanced_ae:adv_pattern_provider]&f"
	task.7058D3373DA87B34.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.7FBDB1383D052B82.title: "ME输出总线 或 &aME接口&f&7[ME Export Bus OR ME Interface]&f"
	quest.1568CBFA09827137.quest_desc: ["与逻辑编程器相同,只是这个可以在任何地方使用.\\n&7[Same thing as Logic Programmer, only this one can be used anywhere.]&f"]
	quest.1B5C86AE05678420.quest_desc: ["当你右键点击一个接口时,会弹出几个选项,以下是它们的功能:\\n\\n&l设置面&r:在屏幕顶部,你可以设置接口”模拟”所在的面.这对于具有特定输入/输出面的机器很有用.\\n\\n&l刻/操作&r:如果接口设置为&a10刻&f/操作,它将每&a10刻&f(0.5秒)导入/导出一次.\\n\\n&l优先级&r:将物品发送到具有更高优先级接口的物品栏.\\n\\n&l物品/能量通道&r:这会将你的系统分成多个通道.你可以从网络中的不同位置推送和拉取物品.\\n&7[When you right-click on an interface, it brings up several options, here's what they all do:\\n\\nlSet Side: At the top of the screen, you can set the side that the interface \"acts\" like it's on. It can be useful for machines with specific input/output sides.\\n\\nlTicks/Operation: If an interface is set to 10 ticks/operation, it will import/export once every 10 ticks (0.5 seconds).\\n\\nlPriority: Sends items to the inventory with the higher priority interface on it.\\n\\nlItem/Energy Channels: This will split your system into multiple channels. You can push and pull from different places in your network.]&f"]
	quest.2F37E284BB83BFF6.quest_desc: ["扳手用于旋转或破坏某些方块,在空中按住Shift右键单击可切换模式.\\n&7[The Wrench is used to rotate or destroy certain blocks, shift right-click in the air to change modes.]&f"]
	quest.33F4A7613764A016.quest_desc: ["工作方式与导入器类似,只是它们进行导出.\\n&7[Works like Importers do, only they export instead.]&f"]
	quest.33F4A7613764A016.quest_subtitle: "导出&7[Exporting]&f"
	quest.3BC94B0B922C0708.quest_desc: ["这些是用于制作导入物品、流体或能量的东西的合成材料.\\n&7[These are crafting ingredients for stuff that does importing, whether it be items, fluids, or energy.]&f"]
	quest.3C9539083BCC145C.quest_desc: ["&a门瑞欧蜜蜂&f可用于自动化水晶化门瑞欧块的生产.\\n&7[Menril Bees can be used to automate Crystallized Menril Chunks.]&f"]
	quest.3C9539083BCC145C.quest_subtitle: "自动化门瑞欧&7[Automating Menril]&f"
	quest.437F4945AFBE0825.quest_desc: ["当你右键点击一个导入器或导出器时,会弹出一个菜单.菜单主要用于过滤,假设你有一个设置为圆石的变量卡,你的导出器将只发送圆石.\\n\\n当你插入变量时,变量旁边有一个小”+”&a向左&f,点击它会打开另一个GUI.在这里,你可以更改传输速率,以便能够发送&d无限&r的物品/流体/能量,以及能够进行一些其他操作.\\n\\n左上角是设置,这些大部分与接口设置相同.\\n\\n注意:延迟可能会限制传输速率.\\n&7[When you right-click on an Importer or an Exporter, it brings up a menu. The menu is mainly for filtering, say you have a Variable Card set to Cobblestone, your Exporter will only send Cobblestone.\\n\\nThere is a little \"+\" to the left of variables when you insert them, clicking on it opens another GUI. In here you can change transfer rates to be able to send INFINITE items/fluids/energy, as well as being able to do some other stuff.\\n\\nOn the top left we have settings, these are for the most part the same thing as the interface settings.\\n\\nNote: Lag may limit transfer rate.]&f"]
	quest.44DA091B53473723.quest_desc: ["&a技工&f挤压器使用能量进行挤压.\\n&7[The Mechanical Squeezer uses energy to squeeze.]&f"]
	quest.450EDE68EC992A5A.quest_desc: ["接口会&c读取&r它们所面向的任何东西.你可以把这想象成一个&bAE2&r存储总线.\\n\\n你不知道那是什么？好吧,举个例子:一个装有100个圆石的箱子,上面有一个接口,这意味着你的ID网络系统中有100个圆石,很简单,对吧？\\n&7[Interfaces read whatever they're looking at. You can think of this like an AE2 Storage Bus.\\n\\nYou don't know what that is? Well here's an example: A chest with 100 Cobblestone in it has an interface on it, this means your ID network has 100 Cobblestone in it's system, pretty simple, right?]&f"]
	quest.450EDE68EC992A5A.quest_subtitle: "接口有GUI!&7[Interfaces Have GUIs!]&f"
	quest.499CF9F39CED8899.quest_desc: ["&b&d动态联合/集成动力&f&r(ID)是一个物流模组,可用于存储、物品/能量/流体传输等更多功能!\\n\\n门瑞欧树苗可以通过使用铁质或更高级的筛网筛苔藓获得.\\n\\n该树还需要一个3x3的泥土区域才能生长.\\n\\n这些任务将涵盖该模组的一些基本概念,如果你想深入了解,请阅读作为此任务奖励给出的指南书.\\n&7[Integrated Dynamics (ID) is a logistics mod that can be used for storage, item/power/fluid transfer and more!\\n\\nMenril Saplings can be obtained by sieving Moss with an Iron+ Mesh.\\n\\nThe tree also requires a 3x3 area of dirt to grow.\\n\\nThese quests will cover some of the basic concepts of the mod, read the guidebook given as a reward for this quest if you want to go further in depth.]&f"]
	quest.499CF9F39CED8899.quest_subtitle: "种植门瑞欧&7[Growing Menril]&f"
	quest.499CF9F39CED8899.title: "&b&d动态联合/集成动力&f&7[Integrated Dynamics]&f"
	quest.4A05C037C0EE40BD.quest_desc: ["逻辑线缆与其他线缆不同.其他线缆充当漏斗,物品从一个物品栏移动到线缆中,然后进入第二个物品栏.逻辑线缆只是跳过了中间环节,这也跳过了很多延迟.\\n\\n它们仅用于连接导入器和接口.\\n&7[Logic Cables are different from other cables. Other Cables act as Hoppers, the items move from 1 Inventory, into the cable, then into the 2nd inventory. Logic Cables just skip the middle man which also skips a lotta lag.\\n\\nThey are just for connecting Importers and Interfaces.]&f"]
	quest.4A05C037C0EE40BD.quest_subtitle: "创建网络&7[Making Networks]&f"
	quest.4A05C037C0EE40BD.title: "逻辑线缆&7[Logic Cables]&f"
	quest.4D4152032F0410D2.quest_desc: ["逻辑编程器允许你设置变量的值.这可以设置为物品和流体以进行过滤,甚至是数值.\\n\\n让我给你一个简单的例子:从左侧选择&b物品&r,将你选择的物品放入弹出的GUI的中心槽位,并将一张&b变量卡&r放入右下角的槽位.如果你然后将那张变量卡放入导入器/导出器,它将只导入/导出那个方块!\\n&7[The Logic Programmer lets you set the value of variables. This can be set to to items and fluids for filtering, or even values. \\n\\nLet me give you a simple example: Select Item from the left side, place an item of choice into the center slot of the GUI that pops up, and place a Variable Card in the bottom right slot. If you then put that variable card in an importer/exporter, it will only import/export that block!]&f"]
	quest.4D4152032F0410D2.quest_subtitle: "进阶内容&7[Getting Advanced]&f"
	quest.4D62C62B523C69EC.quest_desc: ["&a发电机&f使用煤炭等可燃燃料产生FE.\\n&7[The Generator generates FE using burnable fuels like Coal.]&f"]
	quest.4D62C62B523C69EC.quest_subtitle: "提供能量!&7[Providing Energy!]&f"
	quest.56BF647EA84FFF7E.quest_desc: ["显示任何时刻正在进行的合成配方.\\n&7[Shows which crafting recipes are happening at any time.]&f"]
	quest.56BF647EA84FFF7E.quest_subtitle: "显示配方&7[Shows Recipes]&f"
	quest.60D9F04E91171D16.quest_desc: ["这可以作为你变量的箱子,或者实际上可以用于高级网络.\\n\\n如果你想要高级网络,请务必在&e集成动力&r中阅读相关内容.\\n&7[This can act as a Chest for your Variables, or can actually be used in an advanced network.\\n\\nIf you want advanced networks, make sure to read about them in the Dynamics of Integration.]&f"]
	quest.62B4A37CFDECA679.quest_desc: ["&a门瑞欧&f树脂会流向挤压器的两个面.在挤压器旁边放置一个&a烘干池&f会使&a烘干池&f拾取门瑞欧树脂.\\n\\n7.5秒后,门瑞欧树脂会变成一块&a水晶石块&f化的门瑞欧.\\n&7[The Menril Resin will go to 2 sides of the Squeezer. Placing a Drying Basin next to the Squeezer will make the Drying Basin pick up the Menril Resin.\\n\\nAfter 7.5 seconds the Menril Resin will turn into a Block of Crystallized Menril.]&f"]
	quest.65D89991A45BC042.quest_desc: ["在工作台上放置一个合成接口并右键点击它,这会给你一些用于&b变量卡&r的槽位.\\n\\n使用逻辑编程器,在左上角搜索&e配方&r,并创建一个用于自动合成的配方,然后将其保存到一张&b变量卡&r上.如果一个配方&c&l需要&r合成的物品,则为每个这样的物品创建一个配方,然后将所有东西放入合成接口.\\n&7[Place a Crafting Interfaces on a crafting table and right-click on it, this will give you some slots for Variable Cards. \\n\\nUsing the Logic Programmer, search for Recipe in the top left, and create one for autocrafting, then save it to a Variable Card. If a recipe lrequires items that need to be crafted, create a recipe for each of those, then put everything in the Crafting Interface.]&f"]
	quest.65D89991A45BC042.quest_subtitle: "&l&c自&6动&e合&a成&b&7[lAUTO CRAFT]&f"
	quest.65FA86357BC60573.quest_desc: ["是时候把东西从一个地方搬到另一个地方了.步骤如下:\\n\\n&l1.&r 在一个容器(如箱子或储罐)上放置一个接口.\\n\\n&l2.&r 在另一个容器上放置一个输入器或输出器,具体取决于你是想从中拉取物品还是向其发送物品.\\n\\n&l3.&r 用逻辑缆线将两者连接起来,将变量卡放入输入器或输出器中,然后就可以开始工作了!\\n&7[It's time to move stuff from one place to another. Here are the steps:\\n\\nl1. Place an interface on an inventory (like a Chest or a Tank)\\n\\nl2. Place an Importer or an Exporter on another inventory, depending on whether you want to pull or send stuff to it.\\n\\nl3. Hook the both up with Cables, place a Variable Card into the Importer or Exporter, and there you go!]&f"]
	quest.65FA86357BC60573.quest_subtitle: "移动物品!&7[Moving Stuff!]&f"
	quest.68498ADEF9765F81.quest_desc: ["要制作结晶紫晶块,首先需要将一些紫晶原木放入挤压机.跳上挤压机将其转化为紫晶树脂.\\n\\n你可以通过给挤压机一个红石信号来清空它.\\n&7[To make Crystallized Menril Chunks you first need to place some Menril Logs in a Squeezer. Jump on the Squeezer to turn them into Menril Resin.\\n\\nYou can empty the Squeezer by giving it a Redstone signal.]&f"]
	quest.6ABDBE41880CFDA9.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 为 AllTheMods 整合包创作.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 AllTheMods 团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你能看到此信息,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.6C9191DA4B1039D6.quest_desc: ["食用紫晶浆果会给予你短时间的 &a夜视&f 效果.\\n&7[Menril Berries give you Night Vision for a short amount of time when eaten.]&f"]
	quest.6D75CF34957ECCD9.quest_desc: ["&a能量&f 电池可以存储 FE.要传输能量,你需要 &6&a能量接口&f&r.\\n&7[The Energy Battery lets you store FE. To transfer it, you will need Energy Interfaces.]&f"]
	quest.6D75CF34957ECCD9.quest_subtitle: "存储能量&7[Storing Energy]&f"
	quest.72F57D77C3FB366D.quest_desc: ["结晶紫晶块可以合成为结晶紫晶碎片.这些碎片是 ID 的主要合成材料.\\n&7[Blocks of Crystallized Menril can be crafted into Crystallized Menril Chunks. These chunks are the main crafting ingredient of ID.]&f"]
	quest.72F57D77C3FB366D.quest_subtitle: "主要合成材料&7[The Main Crafting Ingredient]&f"
	quest.72F57D77C3FB366D.title: "结晶紫晶碎片&7[Crystallized Menril Chunks]&f"
	quest.73EA326304C01C3B.quest_desc: [
		"将输入器放在你想要拉取物品的容器上.接着,将接口放在第二个容器上,并用逻辑缆线连接它们.然后,将变量卡放入输入器,并按你的需要进行设置.\\n\\n可以将其设置为以整数上限(超过20亿)的数量导入物品.\\n&7[Put an Importer onto the inventory you want stuff pulled from. Next, put the Interface on the second inventory and connect them with Logic Cables. Then, put in the Variable Card into the Importer and change it as you please.\\n\\nIt can be changed to import things at the Integer Limit (Over 2 billion).]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/id_item.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/id_fluid.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/logistics/id_energy.png width:200 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.73EA326304C01C3B.quest_subtitle: "导入&7[Importing]&f"
	quest.7413BB136EF9D6C5.quest_desc: ["&a机械&f 的 &a烘干池&f 使用能量来干燥物品.\\n&7[The Mechanical Drying Basin uses energy to dry]&f"]
	quest.79C1105A84B8BF8F.quest_desc: ["变量卡是启动诸如导入物品等交互所必需的.你需要将它们放入输入器的其中一个插槽中来添加它们.\\n\\n之后,你可以通过 + 按钮编辑所有内容.你可以更改导入数量、物品槽位、频道,几乎所有设置都可以通过这张卡完成.\\n\\n如果你只是想移动物品,不需要太复杂的设置,只需放入卡片,或许可以更改移动数量的上限.\\n&7[Variable Cards are necessary for starting Interactions like Importing Items. You will put them in one of the slots of the Importer to add them.\\n\\nFrom there you can edit everything via the + Button. You can change how much is Importer, which Item Slot, which Channel, practically everything with just that Card.\\n\\nIf you're just wanting to move items, nothing too fancy just put it in and maybe change the Limit for how much is moved.]&f"]
	quest.79C1105A84B8BF8F.title: "变量卡&7[Variable Cards]&f"
	task.166BA23E49F6DCD6.title: "输入器&7[Importers]&f"
	task.1C045BB5FAFCF4D3.title: "接口&7[Interfaces]&f"
	task.1C7C0F345759111C.title: "输出器&7[Exporters]&f"
	task.22CCBBC66D509404.title: "网络!&7[Networks!]&f"
	task.238B5BA2FAE9785B.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.2656ACB55A33D4FE.title: "接口 GUI&7[Interface GUI]&f"
	task.267CE316E1F8FA83.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.4209A06A392362DB.title: "输入器 \\ 输出器 GUI&7[Importer \\\\ Exporter GUI]&f"
	task.5DD862CF56AF7BF9.title: "紫晶原木&7[Menril Logs]&f"
	quest.026C63594F813BCC.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"激活时移除玩家身上所有负面效果,有冷却时间.\\n&7[Removes all negative debuffs from the player when actived, has a cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.0272E58516A0C284.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a矿石矿工&f\\n&7[- Ore Miner]&f"
		"- &a矿石扫描仪&f &4&l已禁用&r&f\\n&7[- Ore Scanner lDISABLED]&f"
		"- 割草机\\n&7[- Lawnmower]&f"
		"- 天空清扫者\\n&7[- Sky Sweeper]&f"
		"- 伐木工\\n&7[- Tree Feller]&f"
		"- 树叶破坏者\\n&7[- Leaf Breaker]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 锤子\\n&7[- Hammer]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.02B0CCD5607FF3B5.quest_desc: ["&a玩家&f 存取器是一个与玩家物品栏交互的箱子.通过 GUI,可以配置玩家存取器的各面,以与玩家的物品栏、副手或盔甲槽交互.\\n&7[The player accessor acts as a chest that interfaces with the player's inventory. Using the GUI the player accessor can have it's sides configured to interface with the player's inventory, off-hand or armor slots.]&f"]
	quest.02B8F50721F12CFF.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"防止玩家受到摔落伤害.\\n&7[Prevents the player from taking fall damage.]&f"
	]
	quest.03ED9B0DFE8B4574.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 心智迷雾\\n&7[- Mind Fog]&f"
		"- 眩晕\\n&7[- Stupefy]&f"
		""
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 熔岩修复\\n&7[- Lava Repair]&f"
	]
	quest.04A1D582003A0D9A.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a速度提升&f\\n&7[- Run Speed]&f"
		"- &a行走速度&f\\n&7[- Walk Speed]&f"
	]
	quest.05056CAA64E3971B.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"使弓射出的箭矢根据你的药水罐施加药水效果.\\n&7[Makes arrows fired by the Bow apply a potion effect based on your Potion Canister.]&f"
	]
	quest.05D8C6EF8FCD6250.quest_desc: [
		"原始凝胶是 JDT 添加的第一阶凝胶,需要主世界的基础材料来合成.\\n&7[Primogel Goo is the first tier of goo added by JDT and requires basic Overworld materials to craft.]&f"
		""
		"已解锁合成:\\n&7[Crafts Unlocked:]&f"
		"- 核源铁锭\\n&7[- Ferricore]&f"
		"- 原初煤炭\\n&7[- Primal Coal]&f"
		""
		"凝胶扩散示例:\\n&7[Goo Spread Example:]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/justdirethings/goo_spread_ferricore.png width:200 height:200 align:center}"
	]
	quest.07655CA904354E9E.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"激活时破坏附近的草和花.\\n&7[Breaks nearby grass and flowers when activated.]&f"
	]
	quest.079A415488A32076.quest_desc: ["烈焰烬质是 JDT 添加的新材料.通过在原初煤炭块上使用二阶或更高阶凝胶进行凝胶扩散来获得烈焰烬质.烈焰烬质矿石受时运影响.\\n&7[Blaze Ember is a new material added by JDT. Blaze Ember is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Primal Coal Blocks using tier two goo or higher. Blaze Ember Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.09485B63483B7A15.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"暂时使附近的敌对生物失去对玩家的仇恨,有冷却时间.\\n&7[Temporarily makes nearby hostile mobs loose agro to the player, has a cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.09D2137B4F42006E.quest_desc: ["蚀空烬质是 JDT 添加的新材料.通过在虚炎煤炭炭块上使用四阶凝胶进行凝胶扩散来获得蚀空烬质.蚀空烬质矿石受时运影响.\\n&7[Eclipse Ember is a new material added by JDT. Eclipse Ember is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Voidflame Coal Blocks using tier four goo. Eclipse Ember Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.0A02DBE226C3F44E.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 心智迷雾\\n&7[- Mind Fog]&f"
		"- 眩晕\\n&7[- Stupefy]&f"
		"- &a夜视&f\\n&7[- Night Vision]&f"
		"- 负面效果移除器\\n&7[- Debuff Remover]&f"
		"- 心智抹除\\n&7[- Mental Obliteration]&f"
	]
	quest.0B485DB737A036E9.quest_desc: ["&a机械设置&f 复制器允许玩家在机器之间复制设置.\\n&7[Machine Settings Copier allows players to copy settings between machines.]&f"]
	quest.0B9BBE2A764631BF.quest_desc: ["&a简易&f 交换器可以将其上方的物品、方块、生物或玩家传送到与其链接的另一个简易交换器.使用核源铁锭扳手来链接交换器.\\n&7[The simple swapper can teleport items, blocks, mobs or players above it to another simple sawper it is linked to. To link swapers use the Ferricore wrench.]&f"]
	quest.0C1D55AA9CC902BD.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 割草机\\n&7[- Lawnmower]&f"
		"- 天空清扫者\\n&7[- Sky Sweeper]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 锤子\\n&7[- Hammer]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.0C2EC56133D3CC6C.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"激活时使玩家暂时免疫伤害,有冷却时间.\\n&7[Temporarily makes the player immune to damage when activated, has a cooldown.]&f"
