	]
	quest.0CBFE2CE53DCACD5.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"Increases the jump height of the player."
	]
	quest.0E3FDD8BB6D17A30.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"激活时破坏附近的树叶.\\n&7[Breaks nearby leaves when activated.]&f"
	]
	quest.0FAF274ADA65B26A.quest_desc: ["传送门流体是一种神秘的绿色流体,对于高级 &a传送枪&f 的运行至关重要.\\n\\n将传送门流体催化剂丢入多态流体会产生不稳定的传送门流体,但不稳定的传送门流体只能存在于末地.使用三阶或更高阶凝胶进行凝胶扩散会将不稳定的传送门流体转化为传送门流体.\\n&7[Portal Fluid is a mysterious green fluid vital in the operation of the Advanced Portal Gun.\\n\\nDropping Portal Fluid Catalyst into Polymorphic Fluid will create Unstable Portal Fluid BUT Unstable Portal Fluid can only exist in the End. Performing Goo Spread with Tier Three goo or higher will convert Unstable Portal Fluid into Portal Fluid.]&f"]
	quest.120DCA89A919C7AF.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"赋予玩家 &a夜视&f 效果.\\n&7[Grants the player Night Vision.]&f"
	]
	quest.1256F280F3669DDA.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"使箭矢在附近的敌人之间连锁弹射.\\n&7[Makes Arrows chain to nearby enemies.]&f"
	]
	quest.132F4671E121C7B8.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"增加行走速度.\\n&7[Increases walking speed.]&f"
	]
	quest.16E02F671FBE9148.quest_desc: ["&a传送门&f 枪是一种使用能量创建两个传送门以在两点之间传送的物品.&a左键&f 射击蓝色传送门,&a右键&f 射击橙色传送门,Shift &a右键&f 移除两个传送门.\\n&7[The Portal Gun is an item that uses power to create two portals to teleport between two points. Left Click shoots a blue portal, Right Click an orange portal and Shift Right Click removes both portals.]&f"]
	quest.1705175C20CE91DD.quest_desc: ["蚀空合金是 JDT 添加的新材料.通过在 &a下界合金块&f 上使用四阶凝胶进行凝胶扩散来获得蚀空合金.蚀空合金矿石受时运影响.\\n&7[Eclipse Alloy is a new material added by JDT. Eclipse Alloy is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Netherite Blocks using tier four goo. Eclipse Alloy Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.1705175C20CE91DD.title: "蚀空合金&7[Eclipse Alloy]&f"
