	quest.1E0C6409B2573CCA.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"地面践踏的升级版本,可以击退并减缓附近的生物,有冷却时间.\\n&7[An upgraded version of Ground Stomp that repels and slows nearby mobs, has a cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.1EA02BA24AF02256.quest_desc: ["日蚀&a合金模板&f用于将Celestigem盔甲和工具升级为蚀空合金,同时保留附魔和已安装的升级.\\n&7[Eclipse Alloy Templates are used to upgrade Celestigem armor and tools to Eclipse Alloy while retaining enchantments and installed upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.1ECFA72CF2BA4B45.quest_desc: ["一个简单的投掷器,你可以配置一次投掷的数量.\\n&7[A simple dropper and you can configure the amount dropped at once.]&f"]
	quest.1FE7C52491E7499B.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a自动跳跃&f\\n&7[- Step Assist]&f"
		"- &a跳跃提升&f\\n&7[- Jump Boost]&f"
		"- 地面践踏\\n&7[- Ground Stomp]&f"
		"- 免疫&a摔落伤害&f\\n&7[- Negate Fall Damage]&f"
	]
	quest.1FFA1DA6A5EA4E70.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a自动跳跃&f\\n&7[- Step Assist]&f"
		"- &a跳跃提升&f\\n&7[- Jump Boost]&f"
		"- 地面践踏\\n&7[- Ground Stomp]&f"
		"- 免疫&a摔落伤害&f\\n&7[- Negate Fall Damage]&f"
		"- 地震\\n&7[- Earthquake]&f"
	]
	quest.200ECDC70E97D254.quest_desc: ["&a燃油罐&fister 是一种储罐,可以用其内部流体填充容器.\\n\\n&a燃油罐&fister 有三种填充模式:\\n\\n - 无\\n - 任意\\n - &d戴尔设备&f\\n&7[Fuel Canister is a tank that can fill containers with the fluid it contains.\\n\\nThe Fuel Canister has three fill modes:\\n\\n - None\\n - Any\\n - Just Dire Things]&f"]
	quest.21147C8CBF98AEB4.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 树木砍伐者\\n&7[- Tree Feller]&f"
		"- 树叶破坏者\\n&7[- Leaf Breaker]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		""
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 熔岩修复\\n&7[- Lava Repair]&f"
	]
	quest.237D11FF5B09BA88.quest_desc: [
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 防踩踏\\n&7[- No Trampling]&f"
		"- 自动收获\\n&7[- Auto Havesting]&f"
		"- 加速作物生长 III\\n&7[- Accelerated Crop Growth III]&f"
		""
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrade:]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.2409EAD96CE3BDF7.quest_desc: ["炽金模板用于将核源铁锭护甲和工具升级为炽金,同时保留附魔和已安装的升级.\\n&7[Blazegold Templates are used to upgrade Ferricore armor and tools to Blazegold while retaining enchantments and installed upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.242F74010488F261.quest_desc: ["&a燃油罐&fister 是一种允许更高效使用燃料的物品.它可以储存 50,000 燃料,每个可燃物品根据其可熔炼的物品数量拥有不同的燃料值.一点燃料足以熔炼一个物品.\\n&7[The Fuel Canister is an item that allows for more efficient use of fuel. It can store 50,000 fuel, each burnable item has a different fuel value depending on the amount of items smelted. One fuel is enough to smelt one item.]&f"]
	quest.24BA4B4EED0A9DBD.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 心智迷雾\\n&7[- Mind Fog]&f"
	]
	quest.25213DBA6E6CEDD2.quest_desc: [
		"暗影脉动粘液是 JDT 添加的第四级也是最终级的粘液,需要远古城市和监守者材料来合成.\\n&7[Shadowpulse Goo is the fourth and final tier of goo added by JDT and requires Ancient City and Warden materials to craft.]&f"
		""
		"已解锁合成:\\n&7[Crafts Unlocked:]&f"
		"- 蚀空合金\\n&7[- Eclipse Alloy]&f"
		"- 蚀空烬质\\n&7[- Eclipse Ember]&f"
		"- 时间水晶\\n&7[- Time Crystal]&f"
	]
	quest.25E915AE1FC53254.quest_desc: ["苍穹晶模板用于将炽金护甲和工具升级为苍穹晶,同时保留附魔和已安装的升级.\\n&7[Celestigem Templates are used to upgrade Blazegold armor and tools to Celestigem while retaining enchantments and installed upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.27FD46A8C958D259.quest_desc: ["死亡召回图腾是一次性使用的物品,允许玩家传送回其死亡地点.\\n&7[Totem of Death Recall is a one time use time that allows a player to teleport back to their location of death.]&f"]
	quest.283D7E65F2AD45F2.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"生物扫描仪的升级版本,激活时对附近的生物施加发光效果.\\n&7[An upgraded version of Mob Scanner that applied Glowing to nearby mobs when activated.]&f"
	]
	quest.2875FACD3BFB0A8E.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"激活时提供少量&a愈合&f,但只能在玩家最近受到伤害或正在受到伤害时激活.\\n&7[Provides minor healing when activated, but can only be actived if the player has recently taken damage or is taking damage.]&f"
	]
	quest.2A01CE9206DD4F8A.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"一次性挖掘相邻的矿石方块,但挖掘时间稍长.\\n&7[Mines adjacent ore blocks all at once, but takes slightly longer to mine.]&f"
	]
	quest.2A919F73CB09CF8B.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a速度提升&f\\n&7[- Run Speed]&f"
		"- &a行走速度&f\\n&7[- Walk Speed]&f"
		"- &a游泳速度&f\\n&7[- Swim Speed]&f"
		"- 诱饵\\n&7[- Decoy]&f"
		"- 相位\\n&7[- Phase]&f"
	]
	quest.2B1BAEC5DAAF9DAC.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 树木砍伐者\\n&7[- Tree Feller]&f"
		"- 树叶破坏者\\n&7[- Leaf Breaker]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.2D86D4403E0F4EB9.quest_desc: [
		"炽金是 JDT 添加的新材料.通过在金块上使用二级或更高级别的粘液进行粘液蔓延来获得炽金.炽金矿石受时运影响.\\n&7[Blazegold is a new material added by JDT. Blazegold is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Gold Blocks using tier two goo or higher. Blazegold Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"
		""
		"炽金赋予工具和护甲熔岩修复的固有能力.熔岩修复,当工具/护甲被丢入熔岩源方块时,会修复该工具/护甲,同时将该源方块转化为黑曜石作为修复的代价.\\n&7[Blazegold grants the intrinsic ability of Lava Repair to tools and Armor. Lava Repair, repairs the tool/armor when dropped into a lava source block, converting the source block into obsidian in exchange for repairing the tool/armor.]&f"
	]
	quest.2D86D4403E0F4EB9.title: "炽金&7[Blazegold]&f"
	quest.2F86FB9E4D49E4B0.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 生物扫描仪\\n&7[- Mob Scanner]&f"
	]
	quest.3138B83ABC2930F9.quest_desc: [
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 防踩踏\\n&7[- No Trampling]&f"
		"- 自动收获\\n&7[- Auto Havesting]&f"
		"- 加速作物生长 IV\\n&7[- Accelerated Crop Growth IV]&f"
		""
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrade:]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.35A78E04092767AD.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 药水箭\\n&7[- Potion Arrow]&f"
		"- 喷溅\\n&7[- Splash]&f"
		"- 滞留\\n&7[- Lingering]&f"
		"- &a归航之箭&f\\n&7[- Homing Arrow]&f"
	]
	quest.37B903620493A354.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 自动烟熏炉\\n&7[- Auto Smoker]&f"
		"- 灼烧伤口\\n&7[- Cauterize Wounds]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
		"- 生物X光\\n&7[- Mob X-Ray]&f"
	]
	quest.3971FF7D044D1FE5.quest_desc: ["护甲能力可以在配置菜单中配置和切换.使用 JDT 工具或法杖打开菜单,点击你的护甲来配置该护甲部件的能力.\\n&7[Armor abilities can be configured and toggled in the configuration menu. Use a JDT tool or wand to open the menu and click on your armor to configure the abilities of that armor piece.]&f"]
	quest.3A471716A29F5172.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"为玩家提供鞘翅,注意此升级提供的鞘翅受行走和&a速度提升&f升级的影响.\\n&7[Provides the player with an Elytra, note the Elytra provided by this upgrade is affected by the Walk and Run Speed upgrades.]&f"
	]
	quest.3AE1811C32B94A66.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"如果玩家着火,则扑灭火焰,有冷却时间.\\n&7[Exingishes the player if they are on fire, has a cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.3B3E3D81843BB358.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"提高奔跑速度.\\n&7[Increases running speed.]&f"
	]
	quest.3BF32843DE3CF3C2.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a速度提升&f\\n&7[- Run Speed]&f"
		"- &a行走速度&f\\n&7[- Walk Speed]&f"
		"- &a游泳速度&f\\n&7[- Swim Speed]&f"
		"- 诱饵\\n&7[- Decoy]&f"
	]
	quest.3C8C80345D3F5FE8.quest_desc: ["物品收集器收集物品并将其存入下方的容器中.\\n&7[The item collecter collects items and deposits them into the inventory below it.]&f"]
	quest.3CBB78C9B8D3665E.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"减少敌对生物的探测范围.\\n&7[Reduces the detection range of hostile mobs.]&f"
	]
	quest.3CFD798362605880.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"使弓射出的药水箭具有喷溅效果,击中区域内的多个目标.\\n&7[Makes Potion Arrows fired by the Bow have a Splash effect, hitting multiple targets in an area.]&f"
	]
	quest.3D9964CB0440DD5A.quest_desc: ["将烈焰烬质丢入多态流体中会生成未精炼的烈焰烬质燃料.使用二级或更高级别的粘液进行粘液蔓延会将未精炼的烈焰烬质燃料转化为烈焰烬质燃料.\\n&7[Dropping Blaze Ember into Polymorphic Fluid will create Unrefined Blaze Ember Fuel. Performing Goo Spread with Tier Two goo or higher will convert Unrefined Blaze Ember Fuel into Blaze Ember Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.3F3559EF5D08B706.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"使箭矢主动追踪目标.\\n&7[Makes Arrows actively seek their targets.]&f"
	]
	quest.40C5C355B6DA1893.quest_desc: ["便携发电机是一种手持发电机,使用可燃物品为玩家物品栏中的物品和工具充电,便携发电机与 &a燃油罐&fister 兼容.\\n&7[The Pocket Generator is a handheld generator that uses burnable items to charge items and tools in the player's inventory, the Pocket Generator is compatible with the Fuel Canister.]&f"]
	quest.41E8C93A44559E48.quest_desc: ["&7悖论机器&r 可以以大量能量和 &a时间流体&r 为代价,对指定区域内的方块和实体拍摄快照；然后可以复制它. \\n\\n许多方块和实体被配置文件列入黑名单,所以无法复制蜜蜂!\\n&7[The Paradox Machine can, for a price of a lot of Power and Time Fluid, take a Snapshot of blocks and entities in the designated area; then it can duplicate it. \\n\\nLots of Blocks and Entities are blacklisted by configs so no duplicating Bees!]&f"]
	quest.433117EEA55B6A54.quest_desc: ["只是一个简单的流体放置器.\\n&7[Just a simple fluid placer.]&f"]
	quest.441F37A95AB66E6B.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 为 AllTheMods 整合包创作. \\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 发布的公开整合包. \\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.4458F8829800A950.quest_desc: ["多态流体是 JDT 中所有流体/燃料的基础.通过将多态催化剂丢入水中来合成多态流体.\\n&7[Polymorphic Fluid is the base of all Fluids / Fuels in JDT. Polymorphic Fluid is crafted by dropping Polymorphic Catalyst into water.]&f"]
	quest.446A37C7FCDACF84.quest_desc: ["虚炎煤炭是 JDT 添加的新材料.通过在烈焰烬质块上使用三级或更高级别的粘液进行粘液蔓延来获得虚炎煤炭.虚空焰 &a煤矿石&f 受时运影响.\\n&7[Voidflame Coal is a new material added by JDT. Voidflame is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Blaze Ember Blocks using tier three goo or higher. Voidflame Coal Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.454662617304E299.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"当应用于护腿时,允许玩家穿过方块.有一个方块标签可以黑名单无法穿过的方块.\\n&7[Allows the player to walk though blocks when applied to leggings. There is a block tag to blacklist blocks from being able to be phased through.]&f"
		"当应用于弓时,允许箭矢穿过墙壁.\\n&7[When applied to a bow, allows arrows to phase through walls.]&f"
	]
	quest.454CA1F8CC198D9D.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a自动跳跃&f\\n&7[- Step Assist]&f"
		"- &a跳跃提升&f\\n&7[- Jump Boost]&f"
	]
	quest.45A25221F54A1DEC.quest_desc: ["核源铁锭扳手允许玩家旋转机器,但也用于将交换器链接在一起.\\n&7[The Ferricore Wrench allows the player to rotate machines, but it is also used to link swappers together.]&f"]
	quest.45D683D7F1A32B04.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"允许工具瞬间挖掘方块.\\n&7[Allows the tool to instantly mine blocks.]&f"
	]
	quest.46E6B1600AA8A61E.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 生物扫描仪\\n&7[- Mob Scanner]&f"
		"- 自动烟熏炉\\n&7[- Auto Smoker]&f"
		"- 灼烧伤口\\n&7[- Cauterize Wounds]&f"
		""
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 熔岩修复\\n&7[- Lava Repair]&f"
	]
	quest.46EE2F9818F8D1D9.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"自动清除被挖掘方块正上方受重力影响的任何方块.\\n&7[Automatically clears any blocks affected by gravity directly above the block mined.]&f"
	]
	quest.4773421DC70009AB.quest_desc: [
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 防踩踏\\n&7[- No Trampling]&f"
		"- 加速作物生长 I\\n&7[- Accelerated Crop Growth I]&f"
	]
	quest.48E4D75FD3145AD6.quest_desc: ["时间流体由悖论机器和时间法杖使用.通过将时间水晶丢入多态流体中获得.\\n\\n对于一个如此难以获得的水晶,我很高兴他们这次给了我们一种简单的流体.\\n&7[Time Fluid is used by the Paradox Machine and Time Wand. It is obtained by dropping a Time Crystal into Polymorphic Fluid.\\n\\nFor a crystal so tough to get, I'm glad they gave us an easy fluid for once.]&f"]
	quest.49636B3C6E6D0C2A.quest_desc: ["没有用途,但看起来很酷.\\n&7[Has no uses, looks cool though.]&f"]
	quest.4987759CF379C1EB.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"当你的物品栏中有时间水晶时,防止你获得缓慢和速度效果.\\n&7[Prevents slowness and speed effects from being given while you have Time Crystals in your inventory.]&f"
	]
	quest.49EF8A4346AEF582.quest_desc: ["将蚀空烬质丢入虚空焰燃料中会生成未精炼的蚀空烬质燃料.使用四级粘液进行粘液蔓延会将未精炼的蚀空烬质燃料转化为蚀空烬质燃料.\\n&7[Dropping Eclipse Ember into Voidflame Fuel will create Unrefined Eclipse Ember Fuel. Performing Goo Spread with Tier Four goo will convert Unrefined Eclipse Ember Fuel into Eclipse Ember Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.4A5937F6E5D06BE1.quest_desc: ["一种简单的液体燃料发电机,使用 JDT 添加的液体燃料运行.\\n&7[A simple liquid fuel generator that runs off the liquid fuels added by JDT.]&f"]
	quest.4ACB72F3A23A5A19.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"&a提升游泳速度&f.\\n&7[Increases swimming speed.]&f"
	]
	quest.4B1E4FC4599DB916.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 无敌\\n&7[- Invulnerability]&f"
		"- 灭火\\n&7[- Extinguish]&f"
		"- 鞘翅\\n&7[- Elytra]&f"
	]
	quest.4B3F20E5C7E3BCFB.quest_desc: ["原始煤是 JDT 添加的新材料.通过在煤矿石上使用一级或更高级别的粘液进行粘液蔓延来获得原始煤.原始 &a煤矿石&f 受时运影响.\\n&7[Primal Coal is a new material added by JDT. Primal Coal is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Coal Blocks using tier one goo or higher. Primal Coal Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.4C54BD57CAB8A54B.quest_desc: [
		"炽焰绽放粘液是 JDT 添加的第二级粘液,需要下界材料来合成.\\n&7[Blazebloom Goo is the second tier of goo added by JDT and requires Nether materials to craft.]&f"
		""
		"已解锁合成:\\n&7[Crafts Unlocked:]&f"
		"- 炽金\\n&7[- Blazegold]&f"
		"- 烈焰烬质\\n&7[- Blaze Ember]&f"
	]
	quest.4D98D2123BD5BFB3.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"一次性挖掘相邻的原木,注意挖掘多个原木时会增加破坏所需时间.\\n&7[Mines adjacent logs all at once, note will increase time taken to break when mining multiple logs.]&f"
	]
	quest.4E03AE15BEF86178.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 生物扫描仪\\n&7[- Mob Scanner]&f"
		"- 自动烟熏炉\\n&7[- Auto Smoker]&f"
		"- 灼烧伤口\\n&7[- Cauterize Wounds]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.4E9B35DCA018FD42.title: "工具升级&7[Tool Upgrades]&f"
	quest.4F9932477EDDCB8E.quest_desc: ["高级&a传送枪&f是&a传送枪&f的升级版本,需要能量和传送液才能操作.与&a传送枪&f不同,高级&a传送枪&f允许玩家在已编码的位置之间传送.使用”V”键(默认按键绑定)可以打开用于编码和选择传送目的地的菜单.\\n&7[The Advanced Portal Gun is the upgraded version of the Portal Gun that requires both power and portal fluid to operate. Unlike the Portal Gun the Advanced Portal Gun allows the player to teleport between locations that have been encoded. Using \"V\" (default keybind) the menu used to encode and select destinations for teleportation.]&f"]
	quest.5054977BD5354561.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 树木砍伐\\n&7[- Tree Feller]&f"
		"- 树叶破坏\\n&7[- Leaf Breaker]&f"
	]
	quest.515C0527226BA50C.quest_desc: [
		"&l能力类型:&r被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l能力功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"赋予玩家创造模式飞行能力.\\n&7[Grants the player creative flight.]&f"
	]
	quest.517F0135926B15EE.quest_desc: ["所有简单机器都带有红石控制功能,有些还带有过滤功能.\\n&7[All simple machines come with redstone control, and some come with filtering.]&f"]
	quest.52EC86E03EB50525.quest_desc: [
		"固有能力:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 熔岩修复\\n&7[- Lava Repair]&f"
		"- 防踩踏\\n&7[- No Trampling]&f"
		"- 自动收获\\n&7[- Auto Harvesting]&f"
		"- 作物加速生长 II\\n&7[- Accelerated Crop Growth II]&f"
	]
	quest.53F9E5CE7EE6F852.quest_desc: ["&a动物&f 捕捉器允许运输生物.可以通过实体标签将生物加入黑名单.\\n&7[The Creature Catcher allows for the transport of mobs. Mobs can be blacklisted via an entity tag.]&f"]
	quest.567005978482235F.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 药水箭\\n&7[- Potion Arrow]&f"
		"- 喷溅\\n&7[- Splash]&f"
		""
		"固有技能:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 熔岩修复\\n&7[- Lava Repair]&f"
	]
	quest.5961C1ED32522BEF.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r \\n&7[lAbility Function: ]&f"
		""
		"生成一个玩家的诱饵,将仇恨从玩家身上引开,有冷却时间.\\n&7[Spawns a decoy of the player that pulls agro away from the player, has a cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.5A1AB1AD7DEFDD9A.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 无敌\\n&7[- Invulnerability]&f"
		"- 灭火\\n&7[- Extinguish]&f"
		"- 鞘翅\\n&7[- Elytra]&f"
		"- 死亡保护\\n&7[- Death Protection]&f"
		"- 飞行\\n&7[- Flight]&f"
		"- 熔岩免疫\\n&7[- Lava Immunity]&f"
		"- 时间保护\\n&7[- Time Protection]&f"
	]
	quest.5A38E9F68570F7F3.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a速度提升&f\\n&7[- Run Speed]&f"
		"- &a行走速度&f\\n&7[- Walk Speed]&f"
		"- &a游泳速度&f\\n&7[- Swim Speed]&f"
		""
		"固有技能:\\n&7[Intrinsic Ability:]&f"
		"- 熔岩能力\\n&7[- Lava Ability]&f"
	]
	quest.5A9436B100FC1E67.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 药水箭\\n&7[- Potion Arrow]&f"
	]
	quest.5B02719C13B1FFE2.quest_desc: [
		"Abilities:\\n&7[Abilities:]&f"
		"- 空气爆发:进一步提升了发射距离.\\n&7[- Air Burst: Further improved launch distance.]&f"
		"- 虚空位移:提升了传送距离.\\n&7[- Void Shift: Improved teleportation distance.]&f"
		"- 蚀日之门:在3x3区域内创建一个可移动的洞,方向取决于目标方块的面.创建的洞的距离可配置.注意蚀日之门对方块实体无效.\\n&7[- Eclipse Gate: Creates a portable hole in a 3x3 area, direction is dependant of the face of the block targeted. Distance of the hole created is configurable. Note Eclipse Gate doesn't work on tile entities.]&f"
	]
	quest.5B910F1389C0B915.quest_desc: [
		"Abilities:\\n&7[Abilities:]&f"
		"- 空气爆发:提升发射距离并消耗FE.\\n&7[- Air Burst: Improved launching distance and conusmes FE.]&f"
		"- 虚空位移:将玩家传送到他们看的方向,过程中消耗FE.\\n&7[- Void Shift: Teleports player in the direction they are looking consuming FE in the process.]&f"
	]
	quest.5BBE8B30ED7518B8.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a矿石矿工&f\\n&7[- Ore Miner]&f"
		"- &a矿石扫描仪&f &4&l已禁用&r&f\\n&7[- Ore Scanner lDISABLED]&f"
	]
	quest.5BD5737703F3F077.quest_desc: ["核源铁锭是JDT添加的一种新材料.核源铁锭是通过使用一级或更高级别的粘液对铁块执行粘液蔓延来获得的.核源铁锭矿石受时运影响.\\n&7[Ferricore is a new material added by JDT. Ferricore is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Iron Blocks using tier one goo or higher. Ferricore Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.5BD5737703F3F077.title: "核源铁锭&7[Ferricore]&f"
	quest.5C6709350BEF4050.quest_desc: [
		"虚空辉凝胶是JDT添加的第三级粘液,需要末地材料来合成.\\n&7[Voidshimmer Goo is the third tier of goo added by JDT and requires End materials to craft.]&f"
		""
		"解锁的合成:\\n&7[Crafts Unlocked:]&f"
		"- 苍穹晶\\n&7[- Celestigem]&f"
		"- 虚空火焰\\n&7[- Void Flame]&f"
	]
	quest.5D4E51471F3939E0.quest_desc: [
		"Abilities:\\n&7[Abilities:]&f"
		"- 空气爆发:将玩家朝他们面对的方向发射,过程中消耗耐久度,更高级别的魔杖会将玩家发射到更远的距离.注意只要玩家手持魔杖,就不会受到摔落伤害.\\n&7[- Air Burst: Launches player in the direction they are facing consuming durability in the progress, higher tier wands launch the player a greater distance. Note the player won't take fall damage as long as they are holding the wand.]&f"
	]
	quest.5EE7D5DE07A83C7D.quest_desc: ["&l技能类型:&r 主动\\n\\n&l技能功能:&r\\n\\n激活时用绿色粒子高亮附近的矿石.\\n\\n&4&l注意此技能已被禁用.&r&f\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active\\n\\nlAbility Function:\\n\\nHighlights nearby ores with green particles when activated.\\n\\nlNOTE THIS ABILITY HAS BEEN DISABLED.]&f"]
	quest.5F5120451BA5B2FE.quest_desc: ["高级机器与其简易变体具有相同功能,但增加了可配置的工作区域、更多过滤槽位并且需要能量.\\n&7[Advanced machines have the same capabilities as their simple variants with the addition of configurable working area, more filter slots and requiring power.]&f"]
	quest.60A4994078500F63.quest_desc: ["苍穹晶是JDT添加的一种新材料.苍穹晶是通过使用三级或更高级别的粘液对钻石块执行粘液蔓延来获得的.苍穹晶矿石受时运影响.\\n&7[Celestigem is a new material added by JDT. Celestigem is acquired by performing Goo Spread on Diamond Blocks using tier three goo or higher. Celestigem Ore is affected by fortune.]&f"]
	quest.61213012615619C5.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"自动烟熏击杀掉落的物品.\\n&7[Automatically smokes items dropped by kills.]&f"
	]
	quest.636854555AD75DC3.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"自动将物品掉落物传送到绑定到工具的容器中.按住Shift &a右击&f容器可绑定工具.注意,当安装在JDT锄头上时,虚空微光/暗影脉冲农田的自动收获能力掉落的物品会被传送到绑定的容器中,此外,如果工具的绑定容器已更改,&a右击&f虚空微光/暗影脉冲农田将重新绑定它们.\\n&7[Automatically teleports item drops to the inventory bound to the tool. Shift Right Clicking the tool on an inventory binds it. Note when on a JDT hoe items dropped by the auto harvest ability of the voidshimmer / shadowpulse farmland are teleported to the bound inventory, also right clicking voidshimmer / shadowpulse farmland will re-bind them if the bound inventory of the tool has been changed.]&f"
	]
	quest.6690AEE064DC2A7C.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"增加一次挖掘的区域.安装在更高级别的工具上时,最大挖掘区域会增加.挖掘区域可以在菜单中配置.\\n&7[Increases area mined at once. When installed on higher tier tools the maximum area mined is increase. Mined area can be configured in the menu.]&f"
	]
	quest.6720F863B907A5F1.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"使弓射出的药水箭具有滞留效果,在一段时间内对区域施加效果.\\n&7[Makes Potion Arrows fired by the bow have a Lingering effect, applying effects to an area over time.]&f"
	]
	quest.6737CB17D562B134.quest_desc: ["只是一个简单的点击器,用给定的物品点击.\\n&7[Just a simple clicker that clicks with the item it is given.]&f"]
	quest.67B87570C340C243.title: "盔甲升级&7[Armor Upgrades]&f"
	quest.6889EFC6CC291463.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"激活时击退附近的生物,有冷却时间.\\n&7[Repels nearby mobs when activated, has a cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.6A4D31194C4CE156.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a矿石矿工&f\\n&7[- Ore Miner]&f"
		"- 割草机\\n&7[- Lawnmower]&f"
		"- 天空清扫者\\n&7[- Sky Sweeper]&f"
		"- 伐木工\\n&7[- Tree Feller]&f"
		"- 树叶破坏者\\n&7[- Leaf Breaker]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 锤子\\n&7[- Hammer]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
		"- X射线\\n&7[- X-Ray]&f"
		"- 瞬间破坏\\n&7[- Instant Break]&f"
	]
	quest.6ADE6F9E004055F7.quest_desc: [
		"时间水晶是JDT添加的一种新材料.它们生长在萌芽时间&a水晶块&f上,这些水晶块是通过对&a紫水晶母岩&f或时间&a水晶块&f执行粘液蔓延而创建的.\\n\\n然而,萌芽时间&a水晶块&f必须从主世界、&a下界&f和末地收集时间才能生长时间&a晶簇&f.你无法破坏或对萌芽时间&a水晶块&f使用精准采集.你必须使用交换器、&a纸板箱&f或剪切粘贴工具来移动它们.\\n\\n一段时间后,萌芽时间&a水晶块&f会耗尽能量,必须再次前往主世界、下界和末地.\\n&7[Time Crystals are a new material added by JDT. These grow on Budding Time Crystal Blocks, which are created by performing goo spread on Budding Amethyst or a Time Crystal Block.\\n\\nHOWEVER, the Budding Time Crystal Block must collect time from the Overworld, the Nether, and The End to be able to grow Time Crystal Clusters. You CANNOT break or use silk touch on the Budding Time Crystal Block. You must use a Swapper, Cardboard Box, or Cut Paste Gadget to move them.\\n\\nAfter a while, the Budding Time Crystal Block will run out of energy, and must go for another trip to the Overworld, Nether, and End.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"To automate this process, look at the video linked in the image above this quest."
	]
	quest.6ADE6F9E004055F7.quest_subtitle: "时间把戏&7[Timey Wimey]&f"
	quest.6D9CFCD81A23BB3B.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"使玩家免疫熔岩.\\n&7[Makes the player immune to lava.]&f"
	]
	quest.6F709652A2B88C78.quest_desc: ["&a能量&f 发射器为其工作范围内的方块提供能量,它只能从底部接收能量.\\n&7[The energy transmitter provides power to blocks within it's working range, it can only accept power from the bottom.]&f"]
	quest.6FD4C60B547F4131.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- &a矿石矿工&f\\n&7[- Ore Miner]&f"
		"- &a矿石扫描仪&f &4&l已禁用&r&f\\n&7[- Ore Scanner lDISABLED]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 锤子\\n&7[- Hammer]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
	]
	quest.703BDCDC88DD813C.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 割草机\\n&7[- Lawnmower]&f"
		"- 天空清扫者\\n&7[- Sky Sweeper]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 锤子\\n&7[- Hammer]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
		"- 瞬间破坏\\n&7[- Instant Break]&f"
	]
	quest.70AD088336748892.quest_desc: ["只是一个简单的煤炭发电机.\\n&7[Just a simple coal generator.]&f"]
	quest.70BF85E2D235BAD5.quest_desc: ["将虚空火焰煤丢入烈焰烬质燃料中会生成未精炼的虚空火焰燃料.使用三级或更高级别的粘液执行粘液蔓延会将未精炼的虚空火焰燃料转化为虚空火焰燃料.\\n&7[Dropping Voidflame Coal into Blaze Ember Fuel will create Unrefined Voidflame Fuel. Performing Goo Spread with Tier Three goo or higher will convert Unrefined Voidflame Fuel into Voidflame Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.70C404E5685E4E91.quest_desc: ["只是一个简单的方块放置器.\\n&7[Just a simple block placer.]&f"]
	quest.71128E508D810DDF.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 药水箭\\n&7[- Potion Arrow]&f"
		"- 喷溅\\n&7[- Splash]&f"
		"- 滞留\\n&7[- Lingering]&f"
		"- &a归航之箭&f\\n&7[- Homing Arrow]&f"
		"- 相位\\n&7[- Phase]&f"
		"- 勇度箭\\n&7[- Yondu Arrow]&f"
	]
	quest.71441DFA05FD73E5.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 心智迷雾\\n&7[- Mind Fog]&f"
		"- 昏迷咒\\n&7[- Stupefy]&f"
		"- &a夜视&f\\n&7[- Night Vision]&f"
	]
	quest.7305EE0F7D73C231.quest_desc: ["空白升级是所有能力的基础.能力分为两种类型:被动和主动.\\n\\n被动能力无需玩家主动输入即可工作,而主动能力只有在玩家在配置菜单中设置的按键触发时才工作,并且主动能力在使用时会消耗耐久度/能量.当安装在更高等级的盔甲上时,主动能力的冷却时间会减少,被动能力的效果会增强.\\n\\n锻造台用于将升级应用到JDT工具和盔甲上.将鼠标悬停在JDT工具或盔甲上时按住Shift键,会显示哪些升级是有效的.\\n&7[Blank Upgrades are the base of all abilities. Abilities are separated into two types, passive and active.\\n\\nPassive abilities require no active input by the player to work, however Active abilities only work when triggered by a keybind players set in the configuration menu, also active abilities consume durability/power when used. When installed on higher tier armor Active abilities have reduced cooldowns and Passived abilities have greater effects.\\n\\nThe smithing table is used to apply upgrades to JDT tools and armor. Holding shift when hovering over JDT tools or armor shows what upgrades are valid.]&f"]
	quest.73552A4BA0687962.quest_desc: ["这些升级可以用于工具或盔甲.\\n&7[These upgrades can go into either tools or armor.]&f"]
	quest.7464CA1290B3474B.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 无敌\\n&7[- Invulnerability]&f"
	]
	quest.76B1C5AFC5D6B7CF.quest_desc: ["时间魔杖可用于加速方块,类似于瓶中时信,最高可达256倍速度.与瓶中时信不同,它使用FE和时间流体作为燃料,而不是存储的时间,这使得补充燃料要容易得多.\\n\\n不过,它对假玩家是黑名单的.我们不希望你自动化这个.\\n&7[The Time Wand can be used to accelerate blocks, similarly to the Time in a Bottle, up to x256 speed. Unlike TIAB, it uses FE and Time Fluid rather than stored time as fuel, making it considerably easier to refill.\\n\\nIt is blacklisted for fake players, though. We don't want you automating THIS.]&f"]
	quest.76B1C5AFC5D6B7CF.quest_subtitle: "瓶中时信的近亲&7[Cousin of the Time in a Bottle]&f"
	quest.78840993C7832E89.quest_desc: [
		"有效升级:\\n&7[Valid Upgrades:]&f"
		"- 伐木工\\n&7[- Tree Feller]&f"
		"- 树叶破坏者\\n&7[- Leaf Breaker]&f"
		"- &a自动烧炼&fer\\n&7[- Auto Smelter]&f"
		"- 掉落物传送器\\n&7[- Drops Teleporter]&f"
		"- 瞬间破坏\\n&7[- Instant Break]&f"
	]
	quest.79BBCC1BEE90DBBB.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 被动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Passive]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"允许玩家免于死亡,有很长的冷却时间.所以本质上是一个有冷却时间且不会被消耗的不死图腾.\\n&7[Allows the player to cheat death, has a very long cooldown. So otherwise a Totem of Undying with a cooldown that isn't consumed.]&f"
	]
	quest.7AEFF81E7C8CF300.quest_desc: ["手持JDT工具或魔杖时使用Shift &a右击&f将打开配置菜单,玩家可以在其中配置和切换技能.\\n&7[Using Shift Right Click when holding a JDT tool or wand will open the configuration menu where the player can configure and toggle abilities.]&f"]
	quest.7B9486981786AC47.quest_desc: [
		"&l技能类型:&r 主动\\n&7[lAbility Type: Active]&f"
		""
		"&l技能功能:&r\\n&7[lAbility Function:]&f"
		""
		"永久移除附近生物的AI,由于能量消耗,每次激活最多只能影响五个生物,有很长的冷却时间.\\n&7[Permanently removes the ai of nearby mobs, due to the power cost it can only affect five mobs at max per activation, has a very long cooldown.]&f"
	]
	quest.7D1D2A4E07E98709.quest_desc: ["一个简单的方块破坏器,需要工具来破坏方块.\\n&7[A simple block breaker that requires a tool to break blocks.]&f"]
	quest.7F0B2D58361FB00E.quest_desc: ["&d戴尔设备&f 是一个多面手模组.&d戴尔设备&f 添加了一种称为粘液蔓延的新合成机制,以及协助自动化粘液蔓延和其他实用程序的机器.\\n&7[Just Dire Things is a jack of all trades mod. Just Dire Things adds a new crafting mechanic called Goo Spread, along with machines that assist in the automation of Goo Spread and other utilities.]&f"]
	quest.7F0B2D58361FB00E.title: "&d戴尔设备&f&7[Just Dire Things]&f"
	task.00B0A3B14DEB34B9.title: "混合升级&7[Hybrid Upgrades]&f"
	task.03982D782B426ABB.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.19931057AAC1A03A.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.32309011F80C0A9E.title: "注意&7[NOTE]&f"
	task.366CA7D53571A552.title: "实用工具&7[Utilities]&f"
	task.3AC95E8DC4229D17.title: "&d戴尔设备&f&7[Just Dire Things]&f"
	task.3CAD6AD06BE4C3D3.title: "工具&7[Tools]&f"
	task.40B39896B6CD41C6.title: "盔甲&7[Armor]&f"
	task.5AB4103FF540ABB4.title: "流体&7[Fluids]&f"
	task.5DD919AF75C92C8A.title: "工具&7[Tools]&f"
	task.665A5DFA6270ADA6.title: "简易机器&7[Simple Machines]&f"
	task.67B21CF59C3D02E5.title: "高级机器&7[Advanced Machines]&f"
	task.7197FBBA21C0F94A.title: "盔甲&7[Armor]&f"
	quest.001DE8028CAF0A08.quest_desc: ["&5&l&d通用机械&f&r &5机器&r 可能非常吵!\\n\\n让我们阻止它!\\n&7[lMekanism Machines can be pretty loud! \\n\\nLet's stop that!]&f"]
	quest.001DE8028CAF0A08.quest_subtitle: "嘘……太吵了……&7[shhhhh... too loud....]&f"
	quest.001DE8028CAF0A08.title: "消音 &8升级&7[Muffling Upgrade]&f"
	quest.0095422BC87AA135.quest_desc: [
		"又来了？伙计,我们要的是&7锭&f,不是&7团块&f,也不是&7碎片&r!&7锭&r!\\n\\n把那些&7矿石碎片&r扔进&b&l净化器&r,加入&b氧气&r(很可能来自我们之前的&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r)来制作&7矿石团块&r.\\n\\n现在我们只需重复上一级的步骤.&4粉碎&f&7团块&f得到&7脏污粉&r.\\n\\n&d富集&f&7脏污粉&r来清洁它.\\n\\n然后,&6熔炼&f&7粉&f得到我们的&7锭&r!\\n&7[Again? Dude, we want Ingots not Clumps and not Shards! INGOTS! \\n\\nThrow those Ore Shards into a lPurifier with Oxygen (most likely from our previous lElectrolytic Separator) to make Ore Clumps. \\n\\nNow we just repeat steps from previous Tier. Crush the Clumps to get Dirty Dust. \\n\\nEnrich the Dirty Dust to clean it. \\n\\nThen, Smelt the Dust to get our Ingots!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier3_3.png width:250 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0095422BC87AA135.quest_subtitle: "三级矿石处理&7[Tier 3 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.0095422BC87AA135.title: "&7碎片&f,到&7团簇&f,到&7粉&f,到&7锭&7[Shard, to Clump, to Dust, to Ingot]&f"
	quest.01A90E2541C91DB2.quest_desc: ["大多数&5机器&r,至少是简单的那些,都可以使用&8升级组件&r!\\n\\n&8升级组件&r位于GUI的&a右上角&f.这个界面可能有点令人困惑,但别担心,我来解释一下!\\n\\n首先,底部显示的是&8支持的升级&r.清晰的&8升级组件&r是&a支持的&r,而更透明的那些则是&4不支持&r!你也可以将鼠标悬停在它们上方来查看其名称以及是否&a支持&r.\\n\\n&8升级组件&r通过顶部的槽位添加,然后它们会显示在右侧.在这里,你可以点击它们来查看机器中有多少个以及它们的效果!\\n\\n如果你想取出我们的&8升级组件&r,点击你想要取出的那个,然后点击卸载按钮.这会将&8升级组件&r移到底部槽位.\\n&7[Most Machines, atleast the simple ones, can use Upgrades! \\n\\nUpgrades are in the Top Right of the GUI. This screen might be confusing but don't worry I'll explain it! \\n\\nFirst, the bottom shows the Supported Upgrades. The clear Upgrades are Supported while the more transparent ones are not! You can also hover over them with your Mouse to see their names and if they are Supported. \\n\\nUpgrades are added through the Top Slot, they'll then show up in the Right. Here you can Click them to see how many are in the Machine and see their Effect! \\n\\nIf you'd like to take our Upgrades out, Click the one you want out, then hit the Uninstall Button. This will move the Upgrade into the Bottom Slot.]&f"]
	quest.01A90E2541C91DB2.title: "&8机器升级&7[Machine Upgrades]&f"
	quest.041365A540BF5A03.quest_desc: ["&7标签词典&r对普通玩家没什么帮助:它不能挖掘、放置方块、合成、烧炼,基本上不与任何东西交互.\\n\\n相反,它用于查找标签!\\n\\n我们可以手持&7标签词典&a右击&f一个方块,该方块的标签就会在聊天中显示.对实体也可以这样做.\\n\\n这还不够？好吧,我们还可以按住Shift并&a右击打开&f我们的&7标签词典&r!\\n\\n在这里,我们可以看到我们物品栏中的物品,并检查它们所有不同的标签.从物品标签、药水标签到附魔标签,没有什么能逃过&7标签词典&r的法眼!\\n&7[The Dictionary isn't helpful to the average Player: it doesn't Mine, Place Blocks, Craft, Smelt, really interact with anything. \\n\\nInstead it is used for finding Tags! \\n\\nWe can Right Click a Block with the Dictionary in Hand and the Blocks Tags will show up in Chat. We can do the same with Entities. \\n\\nIs that not enough? Well we can also Shift Right Click to open up our Dictionary! \\n\\nHere we can see the Items in our Inventory and check all the different Tags for them. From Item, to Potion, to Enchantment Tags, nothing can hide from the Dictionary!]&f"]
	quest.041365A540BF5A03.title: "&7标签词典&7[Dictionary]&f"
	quest.0498A578D0EC3254.quest_desc: ["最后一个重要的灌注物品是&a基础&a电路板&f&r.\\n\\n它们是通过将20mB的&4红石&r与一个&7&a锇锭&f&r结合制成的.\\n\\n查看&c&a灌注合金&f任务&r,了解如何将&4红石&r添加到&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r中!\\n&7[The last of the important Infused Items is the Basic Control Circuit. \\n\\nThese ones are made by combining 20mB of Redstone with an Osmium Ingot. \\n\\nCheck out the Infused Alloy Quest to learn how to add Redstone to the lMetallurgic Infuser!]&f"]
	quest.0498A578D0EC3254.quest_subtitle: "基础&a电路板&f&7[The Basic Control Circuit]&f"
	quest.06210B6FD0F9989B.quest_desc: ["&d&l终极等级&r是我们能从&5&l&d通用机械&f&r中获得的最好等级!至少在生存模式中是这样.\\n\\n它们将提供最多的槽位,储存最多的&e物品&r,并移动最多的&e物品&r!\\n\\n每个&d&l终极等级&r都需要&d&a原子合金&f&f、&d&a终极控制电路&f&f和&b钻石&r.\\n\\n&d&a原子合金&f&r需要&5&a强化黑曜石&f&r来制造,遵循&7&a锇压缩机&f任务&r来获取它们.但基本上,我们需要用20mb的&5&a强化黑曜石&f&r灌注一个&b&a强化合金&f&r.\\n\\n然后,将2个&d&a原子合金&f&r与1个&b&a精英控制电路&f&r结合,制成&d&a终极控制电路&f&r!\\n&7[lUltimate Tier is the best we can get from lMekanism! Well atleast in Survival. \\n\\nThese will give the most Slots, hold the most Items, and move the most Items! \\n\\nEach lUltimate Tier will need Atomic Alloys, Ultimate Control Circuits, and Diamonds. \\n\\nAtomic Alloys will need Refined Obsidian to create, follow the Osmium Compressor Quest to get those. But basically we'll need to Infuse a Reinforced Alloy with 20mb of Refined Obsidian. \\n\\nThen, combine 2 Atomic Alloys with 1 Elite Control Circuit to make the Ultimate Control Circuit!]&f"]
	quest.06210B6FD0F9989B.title: "&d&l终极等级&7[lUltimate Tier]&f"
	quest.0650996C7818ADB5.quest_desc: ["&6&l&a热力发电机&f&r有两种模式来产生&a能量&r.\\n\\n被动模式:用&c熔岩源&r或流动方块包围&6&l发电机&r,通过产生&6热量&r来被动生成&a能量&r.\\n\\n在顶部放置一个&c熔岩源方块&r,并让它从侧面流下.\\n\\n确保先连接好&b管道&r!\\n\\n主动模式:将可燃材料如&0煤炭&r或&6木头&r放入&6&l发电机&r中,燃料会燃烧以产生&c能量&r.\\n\\n它现在产生320FE/t.\\n&7[The lHeat Generator has 2 modes to generate Energy. \\n\\nPassive: Surrounding the lGenerator with Lava Source or flowing blocks creates passive Energy by creating Heat. \\n\\nPlace one Lava Source Block on top, and let it flow over the sides. \\n\\nMake sure to connect Pipes first!\\n\\nActive: Placing combustible materials such as Coal or Wood into the lGenerator will burn the fuel to create Energy. \\n\\nIt now creates 320FE/t.]&f"]
	quest.0650996C7818ADB5.quest_subtitle: "基础发电&7[Basic Power Gen]&f"
	quest.0650996C7818ADB5.title: "&6&l&a热力发电机&f&7[lHeat Generator]&f"
	quest.07084582F9562740.quest_desc: ["&5&l&d通用机械&f&r有几台专门用于染色的&5机器&r!\\n\\n我们需要使用3台&5机器&r,是的,按顺序!\\n\\n&c&l&a颜料提取器&f&r会从&c红&e黄&a绿&b蓝&r方块中提取颜色并制成颜料!颜料是&c化学品&r,并像其他&c化学品&r一样使用:通过&c管道&f输送并储存在&c化学品储罐&r中.\\n\\n&e&l&a颜料混合器&f&r会取2种颜料并将它们混合成一种新的颜色颜料.这甚至可以制造出专为&5&l&d通用机械&f&r &e物品&r设计的新颜色!\\n\\n&b&l&a喷涂机&f&r会取那些颜料并将其应用到可以&c染&e色&a的&b方块和物品上,对它们进行&c染&e色&b.这甚至对已经&c染&e过&a色&b的物品也有效,这在&2&l原版&r中是做不到的!\\n&7[lMekanism has a couple of Machines just made for Coloring! \\n\\nThere is 3 Machines we'll need to use and yes, in order! \\n\\nThe lPigment Extractor will take the Color out of Dyed Blocks and make a Pigment! Pigments are Chemicals, and are used just like other Chemicals: moved through Tubes and held in Chemical Tanks. \\n\\nlPigment Mixer will take 2 Pigments and combine them into a new Color Pigment. This can even make some new Colors made for lMekanism Items! \\n\\nlPainting Machine will take those Pigments and apply them to Blocks and Items that can be Dyed, to Dye them. This even works on Items that are already Dyed, you can't do that in lVanilla!]&f"]
	quest.07084582F9562740.title: "&c染&e色&a与&b颜料&7[Dyes and Pigments]&f"
	quest.081DC030A0546549.quest_desc: ["&2&a生物燃料&f&r是通过&4粉碎&r一些&2植物&r制成的!所有不同类型的&2植物&r各自提供不同的量!\\n\\n&6&a南瓜派&f&r提供最多的&2&a生物燃料&f&r,但&a&a西瓜片堆&f&r效率最高.\\n\\n&2&a生物燃料&f&r可以有多种不同的用途!我们可以为&2&l生物发电机&r提供&a动力&r,用&2化学品 &a生物燃料&f&r &9&l灌注&r物品,或者...\\n&7[Bio Fuel is made by Crushing up some Plants! All types of different Plants each giving a different amount! \\n\\nPumpkin Pie gives the most Bio Fuel but Melon Slices are most efficient. \\n\\nBio Fuel can be used in a ton of different ways! We can Power a lBio-Generator, lInfuse Items with Chemical Bio Fuel, or...]&f"]
	quest.081DC030A0546549.title: "&4粉碎 &2植物&f以获得&2&a生物燃料&f&7[Crushing Plants to get Bio Fuel]&f"
	quest.08DDE018A804BFE7.quest_desc: ["&d&l&a富集仓&f&r会&d富集&r经过它的&e物品&r.只需将&e物品&r放入&4红色槽位&r,&d富集后的物品&r就会从&9蓝色槽位&r出来.\\n\\n什么是&d富集物品&r？或者说当&e物品&r被&d富集&r时会发生什么？要么我们得到更多它可以制成的&e物品&r,要么改变&e物品&r本身!\\n\\n我们可以从1个矿石得到2个粉末.我们可以从一朵花得到更多染料.我们甚至可以改变&6铜&r的阶段或从&7圆石&r上取下&2苔藓&r!\\n\\n随着&d&l&a富集仓&f&r等级的提升,我们会得到更多槽位,可以一次&d富集&f更多&e物品&r.\\n\\n我们还获得了自动分类的能力.按下这个按钮!我们可以设置它,使&e物品&r的堆叠会均匀分布到每个槽位,这样&d&l机器&r效率更高.\\n&7[The lEnrichment Chamber will Enrich Items that go through it. Just place the Items in the Red Slots and the Enriched Items will come out of the Blue Slots. \\n\\nWhat is an Enriched Item? Or what happens when an Item gets Enriched? Either we get more of it the Items it can be made into or change the Item themselves! \\n\\nWe can get 2 Dust from 1 Ore. We can get more Dyes from one Flower. We can even change Copper Stages or take Moss off Cobblestone! \\n\\nWith later Tiers of lEnrichment Chambers we get even more Slots to Enrich more Items at once. \\n\\nWe also get the ability to Auto-Sort. With the press of this Button! We can set it so the Stacks of Items will be evenly distributed to each Slot so the lMachine is more Efficient.]&f"]
	quest.08DDE018A804BFE7.quest_subtitle: "将&a粗矿&f分解成粉末&7[Breaks Raw Ores into Dusts]&f"
	quest.08DDE018A804BFE7.title: "&d&l&a富集仓&f&7[lEnrichment Chamber]&f"
	quest.090B564935D7A8F5.quest_desc: ["不喜欢拆下你的&5机器&r来升级它们？为什么不直接用&e物品&r呢!\\n\\n使用&7等级&r安装器,你只需在&5机器&r上使用&e物品&r就能升级它们!\\n\\n将&a&l基础等级 &r&a安装器&r扔到默认的&5机器&r上,将它们升级到&a&l基础等级&r.\\n\\n不,你不能跳过升级.不能用一个&d安装器&r把&a&l基础&r变成&d&l终极&r.\\n&7[Don't like picking up your Machines to Upgrade them? Why not just use an Item! \\n\\nWith Tier Installers you can just use the Item on the Machine to Upgrade them! \\n\\nThrow the lBasic Tier Installer onto a Default Machine to upgrade them to lBasic Tier. \\n\\nNo, you can't skip upgrades. Can't turn a lBasic into lUltimate with one Installer.]&f"]
	quest.090B564935D7A8F5.title: "&l等级&r安装器&7[lTier Installers]&f"
	quest.09830BB2A23E94B4.quest_desc: ["一些&5机器&r会使用&c化学品&r,特别是用来添加到&e物品&r中.想想&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r、&c&l化学品灌注器&r和&b&l净化仓&r.\\n\\n这些机器基本上会用更少的&c化学品&r完成相同的任务!\\n\\n我不能保证它对每个&e物品&r和&5机器&r都有效.而且不,我不会用每台机器测试!\\n&7[Some Machines will use Chemicals especially to add to Items. Think, lMetallurgic Infuser, lChemical Injector, and lPurifiers. \\n\\nThese will basically use less Chemicals for the same Tasks! \\n\\nI can't promise it'll work with every Item and Machine. And no, I am not testing with every Machine!]&f"]
	quest.09830BB2A23E94B4.title: "&c化学品 &8升级&7[Chemical Upgrade]&f"
	quest.0AA9EF3981E9BA37.quest_desc: ["&a&a能量板&f&r储存的&a能量&r不够？那么,你需要一些&a能量立方&r!\\n\\n&a能量立方&r可以通过电缆输入和输出&a能量&r.每个都有一个固定的&a能量&r存储量,由其等级决定.\\n\\n&a能量立方&r的所有面都可以接收或输出&a能量&r,这取决于电缆是推送还是拉取.\\n\\n&a&l基础&r:储存1.6mFE.\\n\\n&c&l高级&r:储存6.4mFE.\\n\\n&b&l精英&r:储存25.6mFE.\\n\\n&d&l终极&r:储存102.4mFE.\\n&7[Energy Tablets not holding enough Energy? Then, you'll need some Energy Cubes! \\n\\nEnergy Cubes can have Energy Cabled in and out of it. Each has a set amount of storage for Energy that is determined by their Tier. \\n\\nAll sides of an Energy Cube can take or place Energy, that is determined by whether Cables are Pushing or Pulling. \\n\\nlBasic: will hold 1.6mFE. \\n\\nlAdvanced: will hold 6.4mFE. \\n\\nlElite: will hold 25.6mFE. \\n\\nlUltimate: will hold 102.4mFE.]&f"]
	quest.0AA9EF3981E9BA37.title: "&a能量立方&7[Energy Cubes]&f"
	quest.0ACE573560A19309.quest_desc: ["几乎每台&5机器&r都会使用&a能量&r,而当我们有几十台时...这对我们的电网来说绝对不容易.\\n\\n如果我们添加&a能量 &8升级&r,&5机器&r会执行相同的任务,只是现在完成所需的&a能量&r更少!\\n要是我们能把这些装在&d&lS.P.S.&r上就好了!\\n&7[Almost every Machine will use Energy, and when we got dozens of them... it's definitely not easy on our Grids. \\n\\nIf we add Energy Upgrades, the Machines will do the same Task, just now requiring less Energy to complete! \\nIf only we can put these on the lS.P.S.!]&f"]
	quest.0ACE573560A19309.title: "&a能量 &8升级&7[Energy Upgrade]&f"
	quest.0E175356D43E6A10.quest_desc: [
		"很好很好,现在我们有了&e氯气&r.制作&3&a氯化氢&f&r还需要什么？哦对了,氢气!\\n\\n像第一级那样,给&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r喂一些&9水&r,得到氢气和&b氧气&r.只是这次我们需要保留氢气.\\n\\n使用我们的&a&l&a化学灌注器&f&r,我们可以结合氢气和&e氯气&r来制造&3&a氯化氢&f&r.\\n\\n将&3&a氯化氢&f&r管道输送到&c&l&a化学压射室&f&r中,以&c注入 &7矿石&r来获得&7矿石碎片&r.\\n\\n&7矿石方块&r会得到4个&7矿石碎片&r,而3个&7&a粗矿&f&f会得到8个&7矿石碎片&r.\\n&7[Good good, now we got Chlorine. What else do we need for Hydrogen Chloride? Oh yeah, Hydrogen! \\n\\nFeed some Water to an lElectrolytic Separator, like in Tier 1, to get Hydrogen and Oxygen. Just this time we need to keep the Hydrogen. \\n\\nWith our lChemical Infuser we can combine Hydrogen and Chlorine to make Hydrogen Chloride. \\n\\nPipe that Hydrogen Chloride into a lChemical Injection Chamber to Inject Ores to get Shards. \\n\\nOre Blocks will get 4 Ore Shards while 3 Raw Ores will get 8 Ore Shards.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier3_2.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0E175356D43E6A10.quest_subtitle: "第三级矿石处理&7[Tier 3 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.0E175356D43E6A10.title: "&c注入 &3&a氯化氢&f&7[Injecting Hydrogen Chloride]&f"
	quest.0F326EEEC2EBE4E5.quest_desc: [
		"使用&d&l&a富集仓&f&r,你可以&d富集 &e物品&r,将它们转化为&d富集&r变体.\\n&7[Using the lEnrichment Chamber, you can Enrich Items to convert them into Enriched variants.]&f"
		""
		"这些&d富集物品&r在&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r中能提供8倍的mb量.\\n&7[These Enriched Items give 8x the amount of mb in a lMetallurgic Infuser.]&f"
		""
		"&d富集 &0煤炭&r将有助于制造更多&8钢&r.&d富集 &4红石&r将有助于&c&a灌注合金&f&r和&a基础 &a电路板&f&r.而&d富集 &5&a强化黑曜石&f&r将有助于制造&d终极&r物品!\\n&7[Enriched Coal will help make more Steel. Enriched Redstone will help with Infused Alloys and Basic Control Circuits. And Enriched Refined Obsidian will help make Ultimate Items!]&f"
	]
	quest.0F326EEEC2EBE4E5.quest_subtitle: "先富集你的物品!&7[Enrich your items first!]&f"
	quest.0F326EEEC2EBE4E5.title: "&d富集物品&7[Enriched Items]&f"
	quest.109310AF19AAC482.quest_desc: ["&4火焰喷射器&r是&5&l&d通用机械&f&r提供的&a远程武器&f之一.\\n\\n像&c喷气背包&r一样,它使用氢气作为燃料,并且装载方式与&c喷气背包&r相同.\\n\\n我们可以按(N)键来改变它的模式.\\n\\n&e战斗&r:会点燃生物的&6火焰&r并造成&a伤害&f,但不会燃烧方块或物品.\\n&6加热&r:据我所知只能做同样的事.\\n\\n&4炼狱&r:燃烧一切!\\n&7[The Flamethrower is one of the Ranged Weapons lMekanism offers. \\n\\nLike the Jetpack it uses Hydrogen as Fuel and is loaded just the same way as the Jetpack. \\n\\nWe can press (N) to change its modes. \\n\\nCombat: will set Mobs on Fire and do Damage, but won't Burn Blocks or Items. \\nHeat: from what I can tell can only do the same. \\n\\nInferno: Burns everything!]&f"]
	quest.109310AF19AAC482.title: "&4火焰喷射器&7[Flamethrower]&f"
	quest.119BED334E331C25.quest_desc: [
		"最初级也是最简单的&l矿石处理&r只需要2台&5机器&r!&d&l富集仓&r和&6&l冶炼炉&r!\\n\\n我们可以使用&7矿石方块&f得到两倍的&7粉末&f,或者用&7粗矿&f得到多1/3的产量.所以3个&7粗矿&f得到4个&7粉末&r.\\n\\n把&7矿石&r扔进&d&l富集仓&r,你就会得到&7粉末&r!然后,&6烧炼&r那些&7粉末&r得到&7锭&r!\\n\\n恭喜,你刚刚完成了&l矿石处理&r!\\n&7[The very first and simplest lOre Processing is just 2 Machines! lEnrichers and lSmelters! \\n\\nWe can use Ore Blocks to get twice the Dust or Raw Ore to get 1/3 more. So 3 Raw Ore to get 4 Dust. \\n\\nThrow the Ore into the lEnricher and you'll get Dust! Then, Smelt that Dust to get Ingots! \\n\\nCongrats, you just lOre Processed!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier1_1.png width:150 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.119BED334E331C25.quest_subtitle: "第一级矿石处理&7[Tier 1 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.119BED334E331C25.title: "&d富集 &f然后&6烧炼&7[Enrich then Smelt]&f"
	quest.120572510F525930.quest_desc: [
		"&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r是一个多方块结构,它消耗&9水&r,并利用&6热量&r将其转化为&e盐水&r.它还会利用&6热量&r将&e盐水&r转化为&6&a液态锂&f&r!\\n\\n首先,你需要很多&6热力蒸馏方块&r.底座是4x4的,并且必须完全是4x4的&6热力蒸馏方块&r.\\n\\n墙壁至少需要3格高,最多18格.内部和顶部必须像大多数多方块结构一样是空心的.&9水&f和&e盐水&r需要被储存在某个地方.\\n\\n在墙壁内(不包括角落),我们可以放置&6阀门&f和&6控制器&r!&6控制器&r是我们访问&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r图形界面的方式.在那里我们可以看到它拥有的&6热量&r.我们只需要1个&6控制器&r.\\n\\n&6阀门&r是我们移动&9水&f和&e盐水&f进入、&e盐水&f和&6&a液态锂&f&r排出,以及可选地输入&6热量&r的方式!你不需要配置&6阀门&r,只需要配置&b管道&f和&6导线&r.\\n\\n&6&l工厂&r的顶层角落不能用&6热力蒸馏方块&r填满.不过,如果你想获得更多&6热量&r,可以在顶层的角落添加&e&l&o高级&a太阳能发电模块&f&r!\\n&7[The lThermal Evaporation Plant is a Multiblock that takes Water, and uses Heat to make it into Brine. It will also use Heat to make Brine into Liquid Lithium! \\n\\nTo start you'll need a lotta Thermal Evaporation Blocks. The base is 4x4 and only ever 4x4 of Thermal Evaporation Blocks. \\n\\nThe Walls need to be atleast 3 Blocks tall and a max of 18. The inside and top must be hollow like most Multiblocks. The Water and Brine needs to be held somewhere. \\n\\nWithin the Walls (not the corners) we can put our Valves and Controller! The Controller is how we access the lThermal Evaporation Plant's GUI. There we can see the Heat that is has. We'll only need 1 Controller. \\n\\nValves are how we move Water and Brine in, Brine and Liquid Lithium out, and optionally Heat in! You won't need to configure the Valves, only the Pipes and Conductors need to be configured. \\n\\nThe top layer of the lPlant can't have the corners filled in with Thermal Evaporation Blocks. You can add lAdvanced Solar Generators on the corners of the top layer though if you want more Heat!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_thermal1.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"用&6热力方块&r制作一个4x4的底座.\\n&7[Make a 4x4 of Thermal Blocks for the Base.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_thermal2.png width:125 height:100 align:center}"
		"这部分可以是任意大小,只要&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r的高度在3格到18格之间.这也是我们放置&6阀门&f和&6控制器&r的地方.\\n&7[This part can be any size as long as the lThermal Evaporation Plant is between 3 Blocks and 18 Blocks Tall. It is also where we place our Valves and Controllers.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_thermal3.png width:110 height:100 align:center}"
		"&a角点&f必须是空的,或者在顶层填充&l&e&o高级&a太阳能发电模块&f&r.\\n&7[The Corners must be Empty or filled with lAdvanced Solar Generators on the Top Level.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_thermal4.png width:110 height:100 align:center}"
		"当&6控制器&r亮起时,你就知道它设置好了!\\n&7[You'll know it is set when the Controller lights up!]&f"
	]
	quest.120572510F525930.title: "&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&7[lThermal Evaporation Plant]&f"
	quest.162CE44400A63575.quest_desc: ["第一个也是最重要的&5机器&r是&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r!\\n\\n&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r会将一个&e物品&r和一种&c化学品&r结合,以合成新的&e物品&r和合金.\\n\\n&c化学品&f或&a&a灌注类型&f&r将进入&e黄色方块&r,并显示在其左侧的&e进度条&r中.\\n\\n&4红色方块&r将存放被灌注的物品.\\n\\n&9&a深蓝&f方块&r将是产品产出之处!\\n\\n在右侧,&a&a淡绿色&f槽位&r和&a进度条&r用于&a能量&r!\\n\\n如果你需要在&e化学品进度条&r中腾出空间,请使用&l清空&r按钮.这将弹出其中的所有&a化学品&r!\\n&7[The first and most important Machine is the lMetallurgic Infuser! \\n\\nThe lMetallurgic Infuser will combine an Item and a Chemicals to Craft new Items and Alloys. \\n\\nChemicals or Infuse Types will go into the Yellow Square and will show up in the Bar to the Left of it. \\n\\nThe Red Square will hold the Item that gets Infused. \\n\\nThe Dark Blue Square will be where the product goes to! \\n\\nTo the Right, the Light Green Slot and Bar are for Energy! \\n\\nIf you need to make room in the Chemical Bar, use the lDUMP Button. This will eject all Chemicals in it!]&f"]
	quest.162CE44400A63575.quest_subtitle: "起始机器&7[The Starting Machine]&f"
	quest.162CE44400A63575.title: "&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&7[lMetallurgic Infuser]&f"
	quest.166971866A9234C7.quest_desc: ["三种最重要的灌注物品之一是&c&a灌注合金&f&r.\\n\\n要制作它,我们需要用10mB的&4红石&r来灌注一个&6&a铜锭&f&r.\\n\\n你问怎么得到10mB的&4红石&r？把&4红石物品&r放进&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r的&e黄色方格&r里!\\n\\n我们会失去那个&4红石物品&r,不同的&4物品&r会提供不同的量.&a&4红石粉&r&f提供10mB,&4&a富集红石&f&r提供80mB,而一个&4&a块状&f红石&r提供90mB.\\n&7[One of the 3 most important Infused Items is the Infused Alloy. \\n\\nTo make it we'll need to Infuse a Copper Ingot with 10mB of Redstone. \\n\\nHow do we get 10mB of Redstone you ask? By placing a Redstone Item into the Yellow Square of the lMetallurgic Infuser! \\n\\nWe'll lose the Redstone Item and different Items give different amounts. Redstone Dust gives 10mB, Enriched Redstone gives 80mB, and a Block of Redstone gives 90mB.]&f"]
	quest.166971866A9234C7.quest_subtitle: "用于合成物品的基础合金&7[The Basic Alloy for Crafting Items]&f"
	quest.166971866A9234C7.title: "&c&a灌注合金&f&7[Infused Alloy]&f"
	quest.1796E08BBDC09B84.quest_desc: ["&b&l动态&c储罐&r是一种多方块结构,可以制作成任何尺寸,但至少是3x3x3!\\n\\n&b&l动态&c储罐&r可以容纳大量的单一&b流体&r或&c化学品&r.这个&c&l储罐&r能装多少桶&b流体&r或&c化学品&r？这取决于它的尺寸.\\n\\n&b&l动态&c储罐&r由&b动态&c储罐&f方块&r构成,结构内部是空心的.墙壁可以用结构方块或&a反应堆玻璃&f制作,但框架必须由&b动态&c储罐&r方块构成.\\n\\n你还需要在墙壁上安装&b动态&c储罐&r端口来实际输入和输出流体与化学品.它们是输入还是输出取决于它们是推入还是拉出模式.\\n&7[lDynamic Tanks are Multiblocks which can be made at any size that is atleast 3x3x3! \\n\\nlDynamic Tanks will hold a ton of one Fluid or Chemical. How many Buckets of that Fluid or Chemical can the lTank hold? That matters on the size. \\n\\nlDynamic Tanks are made out of Dynamic Tank Blocks with the inside of the Structure being hollow. The Walls can be made with Structure or Reactor Glass but the frame will need to be made of Dynamic Tank Blocks. \\n\\nYou'll also need Dynamic Tank Ports in the Walls to actually take and place Fluids and Chemicals. Whether it takes or places is determined by whether they Push or Pull.]&f"]
	quest.1796E08BBDC09B84.title: "&b&l动态&c储罐&r多方块结构&7[lDynamic Tank Multiblock]&f"
	quest.18783C62009934DB.quest_desc: ["&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r会接收1种&b流体&r并将其分离成2种&c化学品&r!\\n\\n&b流体&r会进入&4红色条&r,而&c化学品&r会出现在&9蓝色&f和&3青色条&r中.\\n\\n我们还在GUI的每个底边得到两个按钮.这些按钮可以切换两个输出条的功能.\\n\\n闲置模式只会达到它能达到的极限,之后就不再接收.所以如果氢气满了,它将不再使用&9水&r.\\n\\n&a排出过量&f模式会达到上限,但会倾倒足够的量以保持生产每种&c化学品&r.这对于那些需要大量&b氧气&r但不需要氢气的人很有帮助.\\n\\n倾倒模式会删除所有生成的该种&c化学品&r.\\n&7[lElectrolytic Separator will take 1 Fluid and split it into 2 Chemicals! \\n\\nThe Fluid will go in the Red Bar and the Chemicals will appear in the Blue and Cyan Bars. \\n\\nWe also get two Buttons on each of the bottom sides of the GUI. These will switch between functions of the two Output Bars. \\n\\nIdle will just reach the limit it can and won't take anymore. So if it is full on Hydrogen it will no longer use Water. \\n\\nDumping Excess will reach the top but will dump enough to keep producing each Chemical. This is helpful for those who need lots of Oxygen but not Hydrogen. \\n\\nDumping will delete all of that Chemical that is made.]&f"]
	quest.18783C62009934DB.title: "&9&l&a电解分离器&f&7[lElectrolytic Separator]&f"
	quest.1922623A26E08078.quest_desc: ["像&b&a流体储罐&f&r一样,但去他的&b流体&r,我们想要其他所有东西!\\n\\n&c加压管道&r能输送的一切,&c化学品储罐&r都能容纳.\\n\\n&a&l基础型&r:可容纳64桶化学品.\\n\\n&c&l高级型&r:可容纳256桶化学品.\\n\\n&b&l精英型&r:可容纳1,024桶化学品.\\n\\n&d&l终极型&r:可容纳8,19&a2桶&f.\\n&7[Like Fluid Tanks but screw Fluids we want everything else! \\n\\nEverything Pressurized Tubes can move, the Chemical Tank can hold. \\n\\nlBasic: will hold 64 Buckets of Chemicals. \\n\\nlAdvanced: will hold 256 Buckets of Chemicals. \\n\\nlElite: will hold 1,024 Buckets of Chemicals. \\n\\nlUltimate: will hold 8,192 Buckets.]&f"]
	quest.1922623A26E08078.title: "&c化学品储罐&7[Chemical Tanks]&f"
	quest.19341B01E048ACAB.quest_desc: ["&a&l基础等级&r是&5机器&r和方块中最简单、最便宜、也是最差的&l等级&r!\\n\\n嗯,除非你把默认&5机器&r算作一个全新的&l等级&r,但我不这么认为.我只是把它和&a&l基础&r算在一起.\\n\\n&5机器&r将从默认等级开始,可以&a增强&f到&a&l基础&r.而其他方块如&b管道&f或&a能量立方&r则从&a&l基础&r等级开始.\\n\\n所有这些都由&4红石&f、&a基础&a电路板&f&f,有时还有&7铁&r制成!\\n&7[lBasic Tier is the simplest, cheapest, and worst lTier of Machines and Blocks! \\n\\nWell unless you count Default Machines as a whole new lTier but I don't. I just count it with lBasic. \\n\\nMachines will start at default and can be Upgraded to lBasic. While other Blocks like Pipes or Energy Cubes will start at lBasic. \\n\\nAll of these are made from Redstone, Basic Control Circuits, and sometimes Iron!]&f"]
	quest.19341B01E048ACAB.title: "&a&l基础等级&7[lBasic Tier]&f"
	quest.195729280394ABFB.quest_desc: ["这台&7&l机器&r能制造两种非常坚固的锭:&e&a强化荧石&f&f和&5&a强化黑曜石&f&r.\\n\\n它用&7锇&r&7灌注&r一个&e物品&r,以创造出更强大的锭.\\n\\n我们需要放入&7&a锇锭&f&f、&7&a锇块&f&f,或者一个装有&7锇化学品&r的&c化学品储罐&f来为&l&7压缩机&r提供&7锇&r!\\n&7[The lMachine creates two really strong ingots: Refined Glowstone and Refined Obsidian.\\n\\nIt Infuses an Item with Osmium to create a more powerful Ingot. \\n\\nWe'll need to place Osmium Ingots, Osmium Blocks, or a Chemical Tank with Osmium Chemical in it to feed the lCompressor Osmium!]&f"]
	quest.195729280394ABFB.quest_subtitle: "真的只对两样东西有用&7[Really Only Good For 2 Things]&f"
	quest.195729280394ABFB.title: "&7&l&a锇压缩机&f&7[lOsmium Compressor]&f"
	quest.1ABD22AA58E093A6.quest_desc: ["只有最好的&5机器&r,才需要最好的材料.\\n\\n使用&d&l终极&r&e物品&r来制造这些&5机器&r以及更多!\\n\\n是的,你会想要这些&5机器&r,它们值得你花费时间和材料!\\n&7[Only the best of the best Machines, will need the best Materials. \\n\\nUse lUltimate Items to make these Machines and more! \\n\\nYes, you'll want these Machines, they are worth the time and Materials!]&f"]
	quest.1ABD22AA58E093A6.title: "一些最好的&5机器&r!&7[Some of the best Machines!]&f"
	quest.1AEFF93A398B8BBF.quest_desc: ["&b&l精英等级&r紧随&c&l高级&r之后.它们拥有和&c&l高级&r相同的增益……只是更多!\\n\\n&b&l精英&r物品由&b&a强化合金&f&f、&b&a精英控制电路&f&f,以及大多数时候的&e&a金锭堆&f&r制成.\\n\\n你可以通过用20mb的&b钻石&r灌注一个&c&a灌注合金&f&r来获得&b&a强化合金&f&r.这相当于2个&b&a钻石粉&f&r或1/4个&b&a富集钻石&f&r!\\n\\n然后你可以用那些&b&a强化合金&f&r(两个)和一个&c高级&a电路板&f&r来制作&b&a精英控制电路&f&r.\\n&7[lElite Tier comes right after lAdvanced. These have the same buffs as lAdvanced... just more! \\n\\nlElite are made with Reinforced Alloys, Elite Control Circuits, and most times Gold Ingots. \\n\\nYou can get Reinforced Alloys from Infusing an Infused Alloy with 20mb of Diamond. That is 2 Diamond Dust or 1/4 Enriched Diamond! \\n\\nYou can then use those Reinforced Alloys (2 of them) with an Advanced Control Circuit to make the Elite Control Circuit. ]&f"]
	quest.1AEFF93A398B8BBF.title: "&b&l精英等级&7[lElite Tier]&f"
	quest.1F8B4F648EB5A0DC.quest_desc: ["抽屉不合你口味？你更喜欢背包？那么你需要一个&a私人箱子&f/木桶!\\n\\n这两者的功能完全一样.合成后,&a右击&f它们将自己设为其使用者.\\n\\n然后,只有你才能打开这个箱子/木桶.哦对了,顺便说一下,你可以从你的物品栏中打开它,或者像普通箱子/木桶一样放置下来打开.\\n\\n它有54个槽位,但没有升级……\\n&7[Drawers not your style? You like Backpacks better? Then you'll need a Personal Chest/Barrel! \\n\\nBoth of these will act the exact same. After Crafting, Right Click with them to set yourself as their User. \\n\\nThen, only you can open this Chest/Barrel. Oh yeah by the way you can open it from your Inventory or by placing it down like a normal Chest/Barrel. \\n\\nIt has 54 Slots but no upgrades...]&f"]
	quest.21D8B88155648EA6.quest_desc: [
		"得了吧,我们都知道你来这是为了什么……&5&l机器&r!\\n\\n&5机器&r是我们的小型工厂,每一个都会在为我们获取更多&e物品&r方面做一些独特的事情.请跟随各个任务来了解每个机器的功能.\\n\\n在这里,我将更多地谈谈配置和&8升级&r!\\n&7[Come on we all know what you are here for... lMACHINES! \\n\\nMachines are our little Factories, each will do something unique in gaining us more Items. Follow the individual Quests to find out what each does. \\n\\nHere I will talk more on the Configs and Upgrades! ]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"所有&5机器&r都不同,但槽位和条的颜色会告诉你它们的用途!&a&a淡绿色&f&f:&a能量&r.&4红色&f:&4初始物品/流体/化学品&f.&9蓝色&f:&9产物&f.&3青色&f:&3第二产物&f.&e黄色&f:&e&a灌注类型&f&r.\\n\\n每个&5机器&r都有默认的配置面.这些是&e物品&r输入和输出的地方.你可以在&5机器&r的GUI中的&a侧面配置&f里更改这些设置.\\n\\n它会为&e物品&f、&b流体&f、&c化学品&f和&a能量&r分别更改,但每个都有类似的可以更改的面.&4红色&f:&5输入&f.&6橙色&f:&6第二输入&f.&9蓝色&f:&9输出&f.&3青色&f:&3第二输出&f.&5紫色&f:&5输入和输出&f.&a&a淡绿色&f&f:&a能量&f.&e黄色&f:&e额外&f,如&c&a灌注类型&f&r.\\n如果你希望&e物品&r能够输入和输出,你需要将GUI设置为自动弹出!\\n&7[All Machines are different but the Colors of Slots and Bars will tell what they are for! Light Green: Energy. Red: Initial Item/Fluid/Chemical. Blue: Product. Cyan: Second Product. Yellow: Infuse Types. \\n\\nEach Machine has default Config Sides. These are where Items will be Input and Output. You can change these in the GUI of the Machine in Side Configs. \\n\\nIt will change for Items, Fluids, Chemicals, and Energy but each has similar Sides that can be changed. Red: Input. Orange: Second Input. Blue: Output. Cyan: Second Output. Purple: Both Input and Output. Light Green: Energy. Yellow: Extra like Infuse Types. \\nYou'll need to set the GUI to Auto-Eject if you want Items to be Input and Output! ]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"一些&5机器&r也可以使用&8升级&r!这些位于GUI的&a右上角&f.\\n\\n在这里你可以看到&5机器&r可以使用哪些&8升级&r.当你放入它们时,它会告诉你它能容纳多少个.&e速度&8升级&r可以容纳更多,而消音升级则不需要更多!\\n&7[Some Machines can also use Upgrades! These are in the Top Right of the GUI. \\n\\nHere you can see which Upgrades the Machine can use. When you put them in it'll tell you how many it can hold. Speed Upgrades can hold more while Muffling doesn't need more!]&f"
	]
	quest.21D8B88155648EA6.title: "&l&5机器&7[lMachines]&f"
	quest.21F3379C904BFD50.quest_desc: ["&6&a电阻型加热器&f&r也会产生&6热量&r,但它不使用熔炉燃料,而是使用&a能量&r!\\n\\n通过给它提供&a能量&r,我们可以选择它产生多少&6热量&r.\\n\\n它产生的&6热量&r越多,消耗的&a能量&r就越多!\\n\\n最大&6热量&r是9,999,999左右.\\n&7[The Resistive Heater will also generate Heat, but instead of using Furnace Fuel, it will use Energy! \\n\\nBy feeding it Energy, we can choose however much Heat it will make. \\n\\nThe more Heat it makes, the more Energy it takes! \\n\\nThe max Heat is 9,999,999 something.]&f"]
	quest.21F3379C904BFD50.title: "&6&a电阻型加热器&f&7[Resistive Heater]&f"
	quest.227E9783382527CA.quest_desc: ["&c&a自由助跑器&f&r与其他盔甲不同,它们使用&a能量&r而不是&c化学燃料&r.\\n\\n当充能并装备在你的脚上时,你可以按下(B)键,它们就会开始工作,你可以再次按下它来&a切换模式&f.\\n\\n&2常规&r:&c&a自由助跑器&f&r会保护你免受&a摔落伤害&f并为你自动跳跃过方块.\\n\\n&6安全&r:会防止&a摔落伤害&f但不会自动跳跃.(首选方法).\\n\\n&4禁用&r:&a自由助跑器&f不会提供保护或自动跳跃,只是看起来很时尚!\\n\\n你也可以升级&c&a自由助跑器&f&r来为它们提供盔甲保护,就像&c喷气背包&r一样.\\n&7[Free Runners are different from the other Armors, these will use Energy instead of a Chemical Fuel. \\n\\nWhen Powered and tied onto your Feet, you can press (B) they will start working and you can press it again to switch it's modes. \\n\\nRegular: the Free Runners will protect you from Fall Damage and Auto-Jump over Blocks for you. \\n\\nSafety: will prevent Fall Damage but won't Auto-Jump. (The preferred Method). \\n\\nDisabled: Free Runners won't protect or Auto-Jump, just look stylish! \\n\\nYou can also Upgrade Free Runners to give them Armor Protection, just like the Jetpack.]&f"]
	quest.227E9783382527CA.title: "&c&a自由助跑器&f&7[Free Runners]&f"
	quest.24BA664B60E49461.quest_desc: ["整个模组化&2&lMinecraft&r中最强大的工具之一!&6&a纸板箱&f&r!\\n\\n这些是用非常简单的材料制成的,只需要4个&6锯末&r.&6锯末&r是通过将&7木棍&r放入&e&l&a精密锯木机&f&r中制成的.\\n\\n现在我们希望有了一个,只需用它&a右击&f一个方块,该方块就会被放入&6&a纸板箱&f&r中.现在我们可以破坏&6&a纸板箱&f&r,通过再次放置它并按住Shift键&a右击&f它&a来移除&f箱子,从而移动方块.\\n\\n有些方块不行,比如&8基岩&r或&d&a末地传送门框架&f&r……但还有很多其他方块可以!比如&5黑曜石&f、&3&a强化深板岩&f&r和刷怪笼!\\n&7[Only one of the most powerful Tools in all of Modded lMinecraft! The Cardboard Box! \\n\\nThese are made with very simple ingredients, just 4 Sawdust. Sawdust is made from putting Sticks into a lPrecision Sawmill. \\n\\nNow that we hopefully have one, just Right Click a Block with it and the Block will be placed into the Cardboard Box. Now we can break the Cardboard Box and move the Block by placing it again and Shift Right Clicking it to remove the Box. \\n\\nSome Blocks won't work like Bedrock or End Portal Frames... but there's so many more that will! Like Obsidian, Reinforced Deepslate, and Spawners! ]&f"]
	quest.24BA664B60E49461.title: "&6&a纸板箱&f&7[Cardboard Box]&f"
	quest.27512B0434531195.quest_desc: ["&c&l&a化学压射室&f&r是另一台&5机器&r,它通过结合&e物品&f和&c化学品&r来工作,但这次只是1个&e物品&r加上1个&c化学品&r来制造1个新的&e物品&r!\\n\\n你可以通过将&9水&r放入&c&l旋转&b冷凝器&r中得到&b&a水蒸气&f&r,然后将&b&a水蒸气&f&r注入死亡的珊瑚中来复活它.\\n\\n你可以从&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r中获得&b氧气&r,并将&b氧气&f注入&6铜&r中来氧化它.\\n\\n最重要的是,使用&3&a氯化氢&f&r注入矿石块中来获得矿石碎片以供加工!\\n&7[The lChemical Injection Chamber is another Machine that works with combining Items and Chemicals, but this time it is just 1 Item plus 1 Chemical to make 1 new Item! \\n\\nYou can get Water Vapor from putting Water into a lRotary Condensator, then Inject that Water Vapor into Dead Coral to revive it. \\n\\nYou can get Oxygen from an lElectrolytic Separator and Inject that Oxygen into Copper to Oxidize it. \\n\\nAnd most important, using Hydrogen Chloride into Ore Blocks to get Ore Shards for Processing!]&f"]
	quest.27512B0434531195.title: "&c&l&a化学压射室&f&7[lChemical Injection Chamber]&f"
	quest.2A793B35FE25003C.quest_desc: ["&l&c旋转&b冷凝器&r可能从&b液体&r中制造&c气体&f,但&c&l化学&e氧化器&r可以将(某些)物品转化为气体!\\n\\n这包括&c&a灌注类型&f&f,如&0煤炭&f到&0碳&r.\\n\\n这也需要用于将废弃蜂巢和&a锂&f蜂巢转化为它们的&c化学品&r!\\n\\n&e物品&r会进入&4红色槽&r,它们新的&c气体&r形态会出现在&9蓝色条&r中.\\n&7[The lRotary Condensator might make Gas from Liquids, but the lChemical Oxidizer can turn (some) Items into Gas! \\n\\nThis includes Infuse Types like Coal to Carbon. \\n\\nThis will also be needed for taking Wasted Combs and Lithium Combs into their Chemicals! \\n\\nItems will go in the Red Slot and their new Gas forms will appear in the Blue Bar.]&f"]
	quest.2A793B35FE25003C.title: "&c&l化学&e氧化器&7[lChemical Oxidizer]&f"
	quest.2D1CBCEC82F1B37D.quest_desc: ["&6&a木料加热器&f&r将通过使用熔炉燃料来产生&6热量&r.\\n\\n原木、&0煤炭&f、&0木炭&r,甚至是&a木剑&f!\\n\\n我无法告诉你它能变得多&6热&r,但你会通过&6加热器&r颜色的变化知道它被&6加热&r了!\\n&7[The Fuelwood Heater will generate Heat by using Furnace Fuels. \\n\\nLogs, Coals, Charcoals, even Wooden Swords! \\n\\nI can't tell you how Hot it can get, but you'll know it is Heated by the Color of the Heater changing!]&f"]
	quest.2D1CBCEC82F1B37D.title: "&6&a木料加热器&f&7[Fuelwood Heater]&f"
	quest.2EA0C74AE7366656.quest_desc: ["&a&a便携式传送器&f&r将允许你传送到任何(已供能的)&a&l传送器&r.\\n\\n当然,它也需要&a能量&r,所以你需要给它充电.并且出于安全原因,&a右击&f它将其设置为你的.\\n\\n在它充好电并属于你之后,你可以右&a键点击打开&f它的GUI.在这里,你可以点击任何网络,然后点击传送按钮传送到那个&a&l传送器&r.\\n\\n不,你不能传送到&a&a便携式传送器&f&r,它是一个物品……\\n&7[The Portable Teleporter will allow you to Teleport to any (Powered) lTeleporter. \\n\\nOf course it does need Energy as well, so you'll need to Charge it. And Right Click it to set it to you for Security reasons. \\n\\nAfter it is Charged and yours, you can Right Click to open its GUI. Here you can Click any Network and hit the Teleport Button to Teleport to that lTeleporter. \\n\\nNo, you can't Teleport to the Portable Teleporter, it's an Item...  ]&f"]
	quest.2EA0C74AE7366656.title: "&a&a便携式传送器&f&7[Portable Teleporter]&f"
	quest.31B73D16C0199785.quest_desc: ["将&5&a强化黑曜石粉&f&r扔进&7&l&a锇压缩机&f&r中,并将一些&7锇&r&7压缩&f进去!\\n\\n我想&7&l&a锇压缩机&f&r就是这么工作的……\\n\\n现在我们将拥有&5&a强化黑曜石锭&f&r,这些可以用来制造其他&5机器&r,甚至工具和盔甲!\\n&7[Throw the Refined Obsidian Dust into an lOsmium Compressor and Compress some Osmium into it! \\n\\nI think that's how the lOsmium Compressor works... \\n\\nNow we'll have Refined Obsidian Ingots, these can be made into other Machines or even Tools and Armor!]&f"]
	quest.31B73D16C0199785.title: "&5&a强化黑曜石&f&7[Refined Obsidian]&f"
	quest.33415CB421F7620A.quest_desc: ["&b&l&a提纯仓&f&r在技术上是对&d&l&a富集仓&f&r的升级.嗯……它失去了很多功能,但它确实升级了&l矿石处理&r!\\n\\n这基本上就是它的全部功能,它将&7矿石&r与&b氧气&r结合,从中获得更多的锭!\\n\\n嗯……它不生产&7锭&r,而是生产&7团簇&r……不管怎样,请阅读&l矿石处理&r任务以了解更多信息!\\n&7[The lPurification Chamber is technically an Upgrade to the lEnrichment Chamber. Well... it loses a lot of functions but it does Upgrade the lOre Processing! \\n\\nThat is pretty much all it does, it combines Ores with Oxygen to get more Ingots out of them! \\n\\nWell... it doesn't make Ingots it makes Clumps... whatever just read the lOre Processing Quest to find out more about that then!]&f"]
	quest.33415CB421F7620A.title: "&b&l&a提纯仓&f&7[lPurification Chamber]&f"
	quest.33C69B5934BE4D64.quest_desc: ["&b机械管道&r将移动&b流体&r.没错!不仅仅是&9水&r!\\n\\n&b机械管道&r由2个&8&a钢锭&f&r和1个&7空桶&r制成.它们的升级方式与&e物流运输器&r相同.\\n\\n&a&l基础&r:可容纳&a2桶&f流体,每刻移动250mB流体.\\n\\n&c&l高级&r:可容纳8桶流体,每刻移动1桶流体.\\n\\n&b&l精英&r:可容纳3&a2桶&f流体,每刻移动8桶流体.\\n\\n&d&l终极&r:可容纳128桶流体,每刻移动3&a2桶&f流体.\\n&7[Mechanical Pipes will move Fluids. That is right! Not just Water! \\n\\nMechanical Pipes are made with 2 Steel Ingots and 1 Empty Bucket. They are also upgraded in the same way as the Logistical Transporters. \\n\\nlBasic: will hold 2 Buckets of Fluids and move 250mB of Fluid each Tick. \\n\\nlAdvanced: will hold 8 Buckets of Fluids and move a Bucket of Fluid each Tick. \\n\\nlElite: will hold 32 Buckets of Fluid and will move 8 Buckets each Tick. \\n\\nlUltimate: will hold 128 Buckets and will move 32 Buckets each Tick.]&f"]
	quest.33C69B5934BE4D64.quest_subtitle: "流体&7[Fluids]&f"
	quest.33C69B5934BE4D64.title: "&b机械管道&7[Mechanical Pipes]&f"
	quest.376532CD98D39781.quest_desc: ["&c&l&a化学灌注器&f&r将取用2种不同的&c化学品&r并……将它们结合.\\n\\n这在游戏早期没什么用,但后期会非常重要!\\n\\n第一种&c化学品&r进入左侧的&4红色进度条&r,第二种&c化学品&r进入右侧的&6橙色进度条&r.\\n\\n是的,它们所处的模式很重要.这是我在&6&l9TTS&r中艰难学到的!\\n&7[lChemical Infuser will take 2 different Chemicals and... combine them. \\n\\nThis isn't helpful early game, but later on it'll be very important! \\n\\nFirst Chemical goes in the Red Bar on the Left and the Second Chemical goes in the Orange Bar on the Right. \\n\\nYes the pattern they are in matters. That I learned the hard way in l9TTS!]&f"]
	quest.376532CD98D39781.title: "&c&l&a化学灌注器&f&7[lChemical Infuser]&f"
	quest.37D4E5ACB35D8BF1.quest_desc: ["&5&l&d通用机械&f&r 的 &c喷气背包&r 工作原理与 &l&7&d&a铁质飞行背包&f&f&r 类似,只是拥有不同的模式,并且需要 &b氢气&r 作为燃料,而非 &a能量&r!\\n\\n只需将一些 &b氢气&r 放入装有氢气的 &5机器&r 中,即可为 &c喷气背包&r 充氢.有趣的是,当 &9&l&a电解分离器&f&r 产生 &b氧气&r 时,也会同时产生 &b氢气&r!\\n\\n一旦将其装备在背上,你可以按 (G) 键在模式之间 &a切换模式&f.\\n\\n&4常规&r:按住跳跃键上升,使用 WASD 键可以向任意方向移动,如果不按 WASD 则只会垂直上升.松开跳跃键时你会下落.\\n\\n&b悬停&r:控制方式与默认模式相同,但移动速度较慢,且松开跳跃键时不会下落.你可以按 (Shift) 键下降.\\n\\n&6矢量&r:不会响应 WASD 键,而是会在按住跳跃键上升时,朝着玩家视角的方向移动.\\n\\n&4禁用&r:不工作!\\n\\n顺便一提,你可以用一些方块和物品升级 &c喷气背包&r,使其获得护甲保护!\\n&7[The lMekanism Jetpack works similar to lIron Jetpacks just with different Modes and it requires Hydrogen as Fuel instead of Energy! \\n\\nJust place some Hydrogen in the Jetpack by putting it in a Machine that has Hydrogen. Funny enough the lElectrolytic Separator also has Hydrogen when it has Oxygen! \\n\\nOnce you strap it on your Back you can press (G) to switch between the Modes. \\n\\nRegular: hold Jump to go up, you will move in any direction you hit with WASD and if you don't you will only go up. When you release Jump Button you will Fall. \\n\\nHover: same controls as Default but with slower movement and you won't Fall when you release Jump. You can lower by hitting (Shift). \\n\\nVector: won't respond to WASD and instead will move to where the Player is looking when holding Jump to go up. \\n\\nDisabled: doesn't work! \\n\\nBy the way, you can upgrade the Jetpack with a few Blocks and Items to make it have Armor Protection!]&f"]
	quest.37D4E5ACB35D8BF1.quest_subtitle: "需要氢气才能工作!&7[Requires Hydrogen to Work!]&f"
	quest.37D4E5ACB35D8BF1.title: "&c喷气背包&7[Jetpack]&f"
	quest.3AF1DC02E9A0010C.quest_desc: ["&c加压管道&r 几乎可以输送其他管道无法输送的任何东西!&c化学品&f、&c颜料&f 和 &c&a灌注类型&f&r 都可以用 &c加压管道&r 输送.\\n\\n不过,为了将 &c化学品&r 输送到 &5机器&r 中,我们需要更改 &5机器&r 内部的配置.这些配置位于机器 GUI 的 &a左上角&f,即 &a侧面配置&f.需要将它们设置为自动弹出到输出端!\\n\\n你可以用 2 个 &8&a钢锭&f&r 和一块玻璃(任何玻璃都行!)来合成它们.然后用 8 个 &c管道&r 和一个 &a电路板&f 来升级它们.\\n\\n&a&l基础型&r:可容纳 4 桶化学品,每刻输送 750mB 化学品.\\n&c&l高级型&r:可容纳 16 桶化学品,每刻输送 &a2桶&f 化学品.\\n\\n&b&l精英型&r:可容纳 256 桶化学品,每刻输送 64 桶化学品.\\n\\n&d&l终极型&r:可容纳 1,024 桶化学品,每刻输送 256 桶化学品.\\n&7[Pressurized Tubes will pretty much anything the other Pipes can't move! Chemicals, Pigments, and Infuse Types are all moved with Pressurized Tubes. \\n\\nIn order to move Chemicals in to Machines though, we'll need to change the Configs within the Machine. Those are in the Top Left of the Machine's GUI, Side Configs. They'll need to bet set to Auto-Eject to Output! \\n\\nYou can Craft them with 2 Steel Ingots and a piece of Glass, any Glass! Then upgrade them with 8 Tubes and a Control Circuit. \\n\\nlBasic: will hold 4 Buckets of Chemicals and move 750mB of Chemicals each Tick. \\nlAdvanced: will hold 16 Buckets of Chemicals and move 2 Buckets of Chemicals each Tick. \\n\\nlElite: will hold 256 Buckets of Chemicals and will move 64 Buckets each Tick. \\n\\nlUltimate: will hold 1,024 Buckets and will move 256 Buckets each Tick.]&f"]
	quest.3AF1DC02E9A0010C.quest_subtitle: "化学品、颜料、&a灌注类型&f&7[Chemicals, Pigments, Infuse Types]&f"
	quest.3AF1DC02E9A0010C.title: "&c加压管道&7[Pressurized Tubes]&f"
	quest.3C8D9278B81BB37A.quest_desc: ["我们没有全世界的时间,让我们 &e加速&r 一下!\\n\\n&2&l反应堆&r 可不会永远等待!\\n&7[We don't have all the time in the World, let's Speed it up a bit! \\n\\nThe lReactors won't wait forever!]&f"]
	quest.3C8D9278B81BB37A.title: "&e速度 &8升级&7[Speed Upgrade]&f"
	quest.424B3E3B299D3999.quest_desc: ["量筒 &8滴管&r 是清除 &c化学品库存&r 的有用工具.\\n\\n在 &5机器&r 的 GUI 中,拿起量筒 &8滴管&r 并将其拖到 &5机器&r 中的 &c化学品&r 上.然后,只需 &a右击&f,它就会移除 &c化学品&r 并将其添加到 &8滴管&r 中.\\n我应该说明一下,我们无法从量筒 &8滴管&r 中取回那些 &c化学品&r.我们只能通过按住 Shift &a右击&f 该物品来清空它.\\n&7[The Gauge Dropper is a useful Tool for clearing out Chemical Inventories. \\n\\nIn a Machine's GUI, pick up the Gauge Dropper and drag it over the Chemicals in the Machine. Then, just Right Click and it'll remove the Chemicals and add them to the Dropper. \\nI should have specified, we can't get those Chemicals back from the Gauge Dropper. We can only Empty it through Shift Right Clicking the Item.]&f"]
	quest.424B3E3B299D3999.title: "量筒 &8滴管&7[Gauge Dropper]&f"
	quest.4274E777FB60BA28.quest_desc: ["&a&l充电板&r 会在玩家踏上 &a&l充电板&r 时,为玩家身上的任何 &e物品&r 充电!\\n\\n显然,它需要内部有 &a能量&r 才能工作.我们可以在 &a&l充电板&r 的背面或底部添加能量.\\n\\n一旦内部有 &a能量&r,它就会为你物品栏中每个可以储存电荷的 &e物品&r 充电!\\n\\n无论它来自哪个模组都一样!\\n它会优先为你物品栏中的第一个 &e物品&r 充电,充满后再为下一个充电.\\n\\n它充满 &e物品&r 的速度似乎对每个 &e物品&r 都是一样的.\\n&7[lChargepads will Charge any Items on the Player when the Player steps onto the lPad! \\n\\nObviously it will need Energy within it to work. We can add that in on the Back or Bottom of the lChargepad. \\n\\nOnce it has Energy within it, it will Charge each Item in your Inventory that can hold a Charge! \\n\\nDoesn't matter the Mod it is from either! \\nIt will prioritize the first Items in your Inventory and once it is full it will Charge the next. \\n\\nHow quickly it fills the Items seems to be the same for every Item.]&f"]
	quest.4274E777FB60BA28.title: "&a&l充电板&7[lChargepad]&f"
	quest.445CC9AAA6F8AAB6.quest_desc: [
		"对于下一级的 &l矿石处理&r,我们将需要 &l&b净化仓&r,而它们需要 &b氧气&r.所以,让我们来制造一些 &b氧气&r 吧!\\n\\n使用一个 &9&l电动泵&r 或任何自动化的 &9水&r 来源,将 &9水&r 输入到 &9&l&a电解分离器&f&r 中.\\n\\n一旦输入 &a能量&f 和 &9水&r,&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r 就会将 H2O 转化为 H(氢气)和 O(&b氧气&r)!\\n\\n我们可以丢弃 &b氢气&r,并将氧气通过管道输入 &b&l净化仓&r.\\n\\n现在 &b&l净化仓&r 有了 &b氧气&r,我们可以将 &7矿石&r 放入其中,从 &7矿石块&f 中获得 3 个 &7矿石团&f,或从 &7粗矿&r 中获得 2 个 &7矿石团&f.\\n&7[For the next Tier of lOre Processing we'll need lPurifiers and they'll need Oxygen. So, let's make some Oxygen! \\n\\nUse an lElectric Pump or any Automated Water to feed Water into an lElectrolytic Separator. \\n\\nOnce fed Energy and Water, the lElectrolytic Separator will turn that H2O into H (Hydrogen) and O (Oxygen)! \\n\\nWe can dump the Hydrogen, and Pipe the Oxygen into the lPurifier. \\n\\nNow that the lPurifier has Oxygen, we can place our Ores into it to get 3 Ore Clumps from Ore Blocks or 2 Ore Clumps from Raw Ore.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier2_1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.445CC9AAA6F8AAB6.quest_subtitle: "二级矿石处理&7[Tier 2 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.445CC9AAA6F8AAB6.title: "为 &b&l净化仓&r 制造 &b氧气&f&7[Making Oxygen for lPurifier]&f"
	quest.47E79DFD123BF617.quest_desc: ["&e潜水套装&r 既是头盔也是胸甲,穿戴时会赋予你 &a&9水下呼吸&f&r 效果!\\n\\n不过,为了获得 &9呼吸&r 能力,我们需要给 &e潜水气罐&r 充入一些 &b氧气&r.只需将其放入装有氧气的 &5机器&r 中,比如 &9&l&a电解分离器&f&r,它就会慢慢充满!\\n\\n然后,戴上 &e潜水面罩&f 和 &e潜水气罐&r,并按 (G) 键将其打开.一旦 &e潜水装备&r 启动,它就会消耗 &b氧气&r,让你能够 &9在水下呼吸&r!\\n&7[The Scube Set is both a Helmet and Chestplate that will give you Water Breathing when worn! \\n\\nIn order to get Breathing though, we'll need to give our Scube Tank some Oxygen. Just place it within a Machine that has some, like an lElectrolytic Separator and it will slowly fill up! \\n\\nThen, put on both the Scube Mask and Scube Tank and press (G) to turn it on. Once the Scube Gear is on, it will use up the Oxygen allowing you to Breath Underwater!]&f"]
	quest.47E79DFD123BF617.title: "&e潜水套装&7[Scuba Set]&f"
	quest.47F38E606AD3FF53.quest_desc: ["一些配方需要 &7&a矿石粉&f&r!\\n\\n多亏了 &6&lAllTheOres&r,我们可以用无数种方法制造 &7&a矿石粉&f&r!\\n\\n&5&l&d通用机械&f&r 的方式是使用 &4&l粉碎机&r 和 &d&l&a富集仓&f&r.\\n\\n我们可以将 &7锭&f &4粉碎&r 成 &7粉&r.或者将 &7矿石块&r &d富集&r 以获得 2 个 &7粉&r.\\n&7[Some Recipes will require Ore Dusts! \\n\\nThanks to lAllTheOres, we can make Ore Dusts in a million different ways! \\n\\nThe lMekanism ways are with the lCrusher and lEnrichment Chamber. \\n\\nWe can Crush Ingots into Dust. Or Enrich Ore Blocks to get 2 Dusts.]&f"]
	quest.47F38E606AD3FF53.title: "&4粉碎&f 成粉!&7[Crushed to Dust!]&f"
	quest.488DBE69595F38F8.quest_desc: ["不,不,不,不,不要再使用 &0煤炭&r 为我们的熔炉供能了,我们需要 &0煤炭&f 来制造 &8钢&r!\\n\\n这里改用 &6&l&a电力熔炼炉&f&r 吧!它使用 &a能量&r 来 &6熔炼&e 物品&r!\\n\\n它还可以被 &a增强&f,以容纳更多槽位进行更多 &6熔炼&r,有点像 &a巨型熔炉&f.\\n\\n&a增强&f&l等级&r 还会有一个自动排序按钮.这允许 &6&l机器&r 自动将 &e物品&r 均匀分配到各个槽位,以提高效率!\\n&7[No, no, no, no, no more using Coal to power our Furnaces, we need Coal for Steel! \\n\\nHere use the lEnergized Smelter instead! It uses Energy to Smelt Items! \\n\\nIt can also be Upgraded to contain more Slots for more Smelting, kinda like a Jumbo Furnace. \\n\\nUpgraded lTiers will also have an Auto-Sort button. This allows the lMachine to automatically distribute the Items evenly among the Slots to be more efficient!]&f"]
	quest.488DBE69595F38F8.quest_subtitle: "&d通用机械&f's &a动力炉&f&7[Mekanism's Powered Furnace]&f"
	quest.488DBE69595F38F8.title: "&6&l&a电力熔炼炉&f&7[lEnergized Smelter]&f"
	quest.4935209D870E25F2.quest_desc: ["90% 的 &5&l&d通用机械&f&r &5机器&r 需要 &a能量&r 才能运行.&5&l&d通用机械&f&r 使用 FE 来驱动 &5机器&r!\\n\\n1kFE 是 1000 FE,1mFE 是 1,000,000 FE!\\n\\n&a&a能量板&f&r 是 &5&l&d通用机械&f&r 的电池版本.它也是合成大多数 &a发电机&r 所必需的.\\n\\n是的,&5&l&d通用机械&f&r 有 &a发电机&r,而且它们非常棒!\\n&7[90% of lMekanism Machines will need Energy to run. lMekanism uses FE to run Machines! \\n\\n1kFE is 1000 FE, and 1mFE is 1,000,000 FE! \\n\\nThe Energy Tablet is lMekanism's version of the Battery. It will also be needed to Craft most Generators. \\n\\nYes, lMekanism has Generators and yes, they are awesome! ]&f"]
	quest.4935209D870E25F2.title: "&a&l能量!&7[lPower!]&f"
	quest.4A1C8125896F7F1A.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 工作人员&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 编写,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.4B35C01F5D0AAC58.quest_desc: ["现在我们有了 &9&l冶金灌注机&r,并且希望有一些 &a能量&r,我们可以开始制造 &8钢&r 了!\\n\\n我们需要在 &e化学品条&r 中有 &0碳&r.我们可以使用 &0煤炭&f、&0木炭&r 或它们的任何变体放入 &e化学品槽&f 来添加 &0碳&r.\\n\\n然后,如果我们将一个 &7&a铁锭&f&f/&7粉&r 放入 &4物品槽&r,它会用 10mB 碳灌注,制成 &a富集铁&f.\\n\\n我们需要重复刚才的步骤,再添加 10mB &0碳&r,将我们的 &7&a富集铁&f&r 变成 &8&a钢粉&f&r!熔炼 &8粉&r 即可得到 &8&a钢锭&f&r.\\n\\n&8钢&r 几乎用于所有东西!机器、工具、升级、反应堆、&a能量单元&f!你会需要很多.\\n&7[Now that we have our lMetallurgic Infusion and hopefully some Energy, we can start making Steel! \\n\\nWe'll need Carbon in our Chemical Bar. We can use Coal, Charcoal, or any variants of those in the Chemical Slot to add Carbon. \\n\\nThen, if we add an Iron Ingot/Dust into the Item Slot, it will Infuse it with 10mB of Carbon to make Enriched Iron. \\n\\nWe'll need to repeat that step just now with adding 10mB of Carbon to turn our Enriched Iron into Steel Dust! Smelt the Dust to get a Steel Ingot. \\n\\nSteel is used for pretty much everything! Machines, Tools, Upgrades, Reactors, Energy Cells! You'll need a lot of it.]&f"]
	quest.4B35C01F5D0AAC58.title: "&8钢&7[Steel ]&f"
	quest.4E7823C2FCEBE4DC.quest_desc: ["只是一把普通的弓,消耗 &a能量&r 而非耐久度.\\n&7[Just a normal Bow that takes Energy instead of Durability.]&f"]
	quest.4E7823C2FCEBE4DC.title: "&3&a电力弓&f&7[Electric Bow]&f"
	quest.4EDD96EB60EF5814.quest_desc: ["如果你在犹豫是否值得制作这个升级,答案是肯定的.\\n\\n&e&l&o高级 &a太阳能发电模块&f&r 会占用更多空间且合成昂贵,但能产生多得多的 &a能量&r.\\n\\n它们的工作原理与普通 &e&l&a太阳能发电模块&f&r 相同,需要 &e白天&f 和 &b天空&r 暴露.\\n\\n这些可以储存 100kFE!\\n\\n你也可以将它们放在 &6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r 顶部以产生更多 &6热量&r.\\n&7[If you're wondering if it is worth making this upgrade, the answer is yes.\\n\\nlAdvanced Solar Generators will take up more Space and are expensive to Craft but will Generate so much more Energy. \\n\\nThey work the same as normal lSolar Generators, Daytime and need Sky Exposure. \\n\\nThese can hold 100kFE! \\n\\nYou can also add them on top of lThermal Evaporation Plants to produce more Heat.]&f"]
	quest.4EDD96EB60EF5814.quest_subtitle: "约产生 480 FE/t&7[Generates about 480FE/t]&f"
	quest.4EDD96EB60EF5814.title: "&l&e&o高级 &a太阳能发电模块&f&7[lAdvanced Solar Generator]&f"
	quest.515A60B89ED5440D.quest_desc: ["&7&a石制发电机&f&r 仅用于 &7&l&a数字型采矿机&f&r.\\n\\n在其中使用时,它们会自动制造 &7石头&r,而无需手动提供.\\n\\n它会用这些 &7石头&r 替换它采集到的矿石!\\n&7[Stone Generator is only for the lDigital Miner. \\n\\nWhen used in it, they will automatically make Stone, instead of needing handouts. \\n\\nIt will use these Stones to replace the Ores it picks up!]&f"]
	quest.515A60B89ED5440D.title: "&7&a石制发电机&f &8升级&7[Stone Generator Upgrade]&f"
	quest.566C1DBA9829E328.quest_desc: ["&e&l合成器&r 可以自动化简单的 2 &e物品&r 配方!\\n\\n比如 2 种不同的染料,或者泥和麦子来获得 &a泥坯&f.\\n\\n它甚至可以做一些新的独特配方,比如 &7圆石&f 和 &0燧石&r 制作 &7沙砾&r,或者 4 个 &5&a黑曜石粉&f &f和 &8深板岩&f 制作 &5黑曜石&r!\\n&7[The lCombiner can automate simple 2 Item Recipes! \\n\\nLike 2 different Dyes, or Mud and Wheat to get Packed Mud. \\n\\nIt can even do some new unique Recipes like Cobble and Flint to make Gravel, or 4 Obsidian Dust and Deepslate to make Obsidian!]&f"]
	quest.566C1DBA9829E328.title: "&e&l合成器&7[lCombiner]&f"
	quest.58B125BD4876054C.quest_desc: ["&5&l&d通用机械&f&r 是一个科技模组,它将改变你玩 &2&lMinecraft&r 的方式.\\n\\n该模组专注于将材料分解为化学成分,并充分利用你遇到的每一种材料.\\n\\n该模组包含氢动力 &c喷气背包&r、一个迷你机器人伙伴、&2&l反应堆&r、一个用于自动化采矿的 &7&l&a数字型采矿机&f&r,以及更多内容.\\n\\n相信我,你会明白为什么它被用于几乎每一个 &6&lATM 整合包&r!\\n&7[lMekanism is a tech mod that will change the way you play lMinecraft. \\n\\nThe mod focuses on breaking down materials to their chemical makeup, and getting the best out of every material you come across.\\n\\nThis mod features Hydrogen-Powered Jetpacks, a mini-robotic friend, lReactors, a lDigital Miner to automate mining, and much, much more. \\n\\nTrust me, you'll see why it is used in almost every lATM Modpack!]&f"]
	quest.58B125BD4876054C.quest_subtitle: "你自己的工厂之始&7[The Start of Your Own Factory]&f"
	quest.58B125BD4876054C.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f&r&7[lMekanism]&f"
	quest.5B556192F060F3F1.quest_desc: ["&5&a强化黑曜石&f&r 对于 &5&l&d通用机械&f&r 中的许多 &e物品&f 和 &5机器&r 都很重要,尤其是在 &d&l终极等级&r.\\n首先,我们需要 &3粉碎&f &5黑曜石&f 以获得 &5&a黑曜石粉&f&r.显然,你需要使用 &4&l粉碎机&r 来完成.\\n\\n然后,我们可以使用 &9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r 用 &b化学钻石&r &9灌注&f &5&a黑曜石粉&f&r.我建议使用 &b&a富集钻石&f&r 以获得最大收益!\\n\\n现在我们有几个选择来处理它,要么 &d富集&r 它以获得更多 &5化学 &a强化黑曜石&f&r,要么...\\n&7[Refined Obsidian will be important for many Items and Machines within lMekanism especially at lUltimate Tier. \\nFirst, we'll need to Crush Obsidian to get Obsidian Dust. Obviously you need to use a lCrusher for that. \\n\\nThen, we can use the lMetallurgic Infuser to Infuse the Obsidian Dust with Chemical Diamond. I'd recommend using Enriched Diamonds to get the most bang for your buck! \\n\\nNow we get a few choices of what to do with it, either Enrich it to get more Chemical Refined Obsidian or...]&f"]
	quest.5B556192F060F3F1.title: "&5&a强化黑曜石粉&f&7[Refined Obsidian Dust]&f"
	quest.5E116409DC7D30BB.quest_desc: ["你现在应该了解物流了!这个任务现在将专门解释&3配置器&r!\\n\\n按住Shift并滚动可以改变&3配置器&r的模式.\\n\\n&d扳手&r:当用于&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的&5机器&r和方块时,会将其掉落.\\n&e旋转&r:将简单地旋转方块的方向.\\n&4清空&r:将使其像&a滴管&f一样工作.\\n其余模式将使&3配置器&r与&5机器&r交互以更改其配置!\\n\\n如果将其用于管道,可以改变它们是推入、拉出还是两者兼具.你可以将其用于端口来设置输入和输出.甚至可以在箱子上设置它们自动导出下方的物品.\\n&7[You should know Logistics by know! This Quest will now be reserved to explaining the Configurator! \\n\\nBy Holding Shift and Scrolling you can change the Mode of the Configurator. \\n\\nWrench: will Drop lMekanism Machines and Blocks when used on them. \\nRotate: will simply Rotate the direction of the Block. \\nEmpty: will make it work like a Gauge Dropper. \\nThe rest of them will make the Configurator interact with Machines to change their Configs! \\n\\nIf you use it on Pipes it will change if they Push, Pull, or Both. You can use it on Ports to set Inputs and Outputs. And even on Bins to set them to Auto-Export below them.]&f"]
	quest.5E116409DC7D30BB.quest_subtitle: "&a配置器&f&7[The Configurator]&f"
	quest.5E116409DC7D30BB.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f&r物流&7[lMekanism Logistics]&f"
	quest.602A6CF9D5B66AD3.quest_desc: ["&5&l&a化学结晶器&f&r实际上是一个非常简单的机器!我们只需要一种&c化学品&f和&a能量&r!\\n\\n是的,这个机器不仅仅用于&l矿石处理&r!嗯,有些是……但不是全部.\\n\\n只需将一些&7纯净矿石浆&r扔进&5&l结晶器&r,它就会将其转化为&7矿石晶体&r.\\n\\n你也可以喂给它&d反物质&r来制造&d&a反物质靶丸&f&r,或者喂给&6锂&r来制造&6&a锂粉&f&r!\\n&7[The lChemical Crystallizer is actually a pretty simple Machine! We just need a Chemical and Energy! \\n\\nAnd yes this one isn't only used for lOre Processing! Well some of it is... but not all. \\n\\nJust throw some Clean Ore Slurry into the lCrystallizer and it will turn it into Ore Crystals. \\n\\nYou can also feed it Antimatter to make Antimatter Pellets, or Lithium to make Lithium Dust!]&f"]
	quest.602A6CF9D5B66AD3.title: "&5&l&a化学结晶器&f&7[lChemical Crystallizer]&f"
	quest.603BEDD49070ECAD.quest_desc: ["&b冷凝&r是将&b液体&f转化为&c气体&r.&c去冷凝&r是将&c气体&f转化为&b液体&r.\\n\\n&c&l旋转&b冷凝器&r两者都能做!\\n\\n&c气体&r将进入左侧的进度条.它们可以通过放置在左侧槽位中的&c管道&f或&c化学品储罐&r添加.\\n\\n&b液体&r将进入右侧的进度条.它们也可以通过放置在右侧槽位中的&b管道&f或&b&a流体储罐&f&r添加.\\n\\n当供能时,&c气体&r将变成&b液体&r,&b液体&r将变成&c气体&r.它们会交换进度条,然后可以通过&c管道&f/&b管道&r或&c化学品&f/&b&a流体储罐&f&r取出.\\n&7[Condensating is to make from Liquid to Gas. Decondensating is turning Gas to Liquid. \\n\\nThe lRotary Condenstrator does both! \\n\\nGas will go in the Bar on the Left. They can be added from Tubes or Chemical Tanks that you place in the Left Slots. \\n\\nLiquids will go in the Right Bar. They can also be added with Pipes or Fluid Tanks placed in the Right Slots. \\n\\nWhen powered, Gas will become Liquid, and Liquid turned into Gas. They will switch Bars and can then be taken out with Tubes/Pipes or Chemical/Fluid Tanks.]&f"]
	quest.603BEDD49070ECAD.title: "&c&l旋转&b冷凝器&7[lRotary Condensentrator]&f"
	quest.60B52705049D1BA5.quest_desc: ["&a&l&a化学清洗机&f&r仅用于&7矿石处理&r.\\n\\n就像&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r一样,这个机器只处理&c化学品&f/&b流体&r!\\n\\n&9水&r(或&9水&r的替代品)将进入左侧进度条!矿石浆将进入旁边的进度条.\\n\\n当提供&a能量&r时,&a&l&a化学清洗机&f&r会将脏浆液变干净!\\n\\n就像&a洗衣机&f一样!\\n&7[The lChemical Washer is only for Ore Processing. \\n\\nLike the lElectrolytic Separator, this one only works with Chemicals/Fluids! \\n\\nWater (or Water replacement) will go in the Left Bar! And the Ore Slurry will go in the Bar next to it. \\n\\nWhen given Energy, the lChemical Washer will make the Dirty Slurry, Clean! \\n\\nLike a Washing Machine!]&f"]
	quest.60B52705049D1BA5.title: "&a&l&a化学清洗机&f&7[lChemical Washer]&f"
	quest.60ECCCAB66AAC05D.quest_desc: ["&e物流传送器&r会将&e物品&f和&e方块&r从一个容器移动到另一个容器!\\n\\n不过,为了将&e物品&r移动到&5机器&r中,我们需要更改&5机器&r内部的配置.这些配置位于&5机器&r GUI的&a左上角&f,即&a侧面配置&f.需要将它们设置为自动弹出以输出&e物品&r.\\n\\n&e物流传送器&r由 2 个&8&a钢锭&f&r和 1 个&a基础&a电路板&f&r合成.然后,你可以将 8 个&e物流传送器&r与下一级的&a电路板&f结合来升级它们.\\n\\n&a&l基础&r:每秒移动 2 个方块/物品,距离为 1 格.\\n\\n&c&l高级&r:每秒移动 32 个方块/物品,距离为 2 格.\\n\\n&b&l精英&r:每秒移动一组物品或方块,距离为 4 格.\\n\\n&d&l终极&r:每秒移动两组物品或方块,距离为 10 格.\\n&7[Logistical Transporters will move Items and Blocks from one Inventory to another! \\n\\nIn order to move Items to Machines though, we'll need to change the Configs within the Machine. Those are in the Top Left of the Machine's GUI, Side Configs. They'll need to be set to Auto-Eject to Output Items. \\n\\nLogistical Transporters are Crafted with 2 Steel Ingots and 1 Basic Control Circuit. You can then combine 8 Logistical Transporters with the next Control Circuit to upgrade them. \\n\\nlBasic: will move 2 Blocks/Items across 1 Block each Second. \\n\\nlAdvanced: will move 32 Blocks/Items across 2 Blocks each Second. \\n\\nlElite: will move a stack of Items or Blocks across 4 Blocks each Second. \\n\\nlUltimate: will move 2 stacks of Items or Blocks across 10 Blocks each Second.]&f"]
	quest.60ECCCAB66AAC05D.quest_subtitle: "物品&7[Items]&f"
	quest.60ECCCAB66AAC05D.title: "&e物流传送器&7[Logistical Transporters]&f"
	quest.6263A27182B2CE3D.quest_desc: ["有些&5机器&r更高级一些,这意味着我们需要更多&c高级物品&r来合成它们!\\n\\n说到&c&l高级&r,它们使用的材料与&c&l高级&r&5机器&r相同.\\n&7[Some Machines are a little more advanced, so that means we'll need more Advanced Items to Craft them! \\n\\nTalking about lAdvanced, they take the same Materials as lAdvanced Tier Machines.]&f"]
	quest.6263A27182B2CE3D.title: "更好的&5机器&7[Better Machines]&f"
	quest.62827AA1AD29A222.quest_desc: ["&a通用电缆&r用于在&5机器&f之间传输&a能量&r!\\n\\n大多数&5机器&r会有一个默认的&a能量&r接收面,由机器上的&a绿色方块&r指示.这些可以在&5机器&r GUI的&a侧面配置&f中更改.\\n\\n如果配置设置得当,&5机器&r还会与相邻的其他&5机器&r共享它们内部的&a能量&r!\\n\\n&a通用电缆&r由 2 个&8&a钢锭&f&r和 1 个&a&4红石粉&r&f制成.可以通过将 8 个同等级的电缆与一个&a&a电路板&f&r结合来升级!\\n\\n&a&l基础&r:每刻存储和传输 3.2kFE.\\n\\n&c&l高级&r:每刻存储和传输 51.2kFE.\\n\\n&b&l精英&r:每刻存储和传输 409.6kFE.\\n\\n&d&l终极&r:每刻存储和传输 3.27mFE.\\n&7[Universal Cables are used to move Energy from Machine to Machine! \\n\\nMost Machines will have a default Energy taking Side notified by the Green Square on them. These can be changed within the GUI of the Machine in Side Configs. \\n\\nMachines will also share the Energy they have in them with other Machines next to them, if their Configs are set to it!\\n\\nUniversal Cables are made with 2 Steel Ingots and a Redstone Dust. They can be upgraded by combining 8 of the same Tier with a Control Circuit! \\n\\nlBasic: will hold and move 3.2kFE per Tick. \\n\\nlAdvanced: will hold and move 51.2kFE per Tick. \\n\\nlElite: will hold and move 409.6kFE per Tick. \\n\\nlUltimate: will hold and move 3.27mFE per Tick.]&f"]
	quest.62827AA1AD29A222.title: "&a通用电缆&7[Universal Cables]&f"
	quest.66A450CAC07232E1.quest_desc: ["&6热力学导体&r会传输&6热量&r.是的,一些&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的&5机器&r使用&6热量&r!比如&6&l热力蒸发装置&r.\\n\\n大多数&6加热器&r会设置好输出&6热量&r的面!\\n\\n我不确定这些数字是什么意思,但遵循这个规律:越贵,越好!\\n&7[Thermodynamic Conductors will move Heat. Yeah, some lMekanism Machines use Heat! Like the lThermal Evaporation Machine. \\n\\nMost of the Heaters will have set Sides for Outputting Heat! \\n\\nI'm not sure what these numbers mean but following the pattern: more expensive, more good!]&f"]
	quest.66A450CAC07232E1.quest_subtitle: "热量&7[Heat]&f"
	quest.66A450CAC07232E1.title: "&6热力学导体&7[Thermodynamic Conductors]&f"
	quest.67E7A9A65B14C933.quest_desc: [
		"我们得到了&7矿石团块&r？我们拿&7团块&r怎么办,我们想要的是&7锭&r!\\n\\n首先,&4粉碎&f每个&7团块&f以获得 1 个&7肮脏的&a矿石粉&f&r.\\n\\n我们不能&6熔炼&7肮脏的粉&r,那会毁掉熔炉!所以我们需要&d富集&r它们来获得普通的&7粉&r.\\n\\n然后像往常一样,&6熔炼&f&7粉&f以获得&7锭&r.\\n&7[We got Ore Clumps? What do we do with a Clump, we wanted Ingots! \\n\\nTo start, Crush each Clump to get 1 Dirty Ore Dust. \\n\\nWe can't Smelt Dirty Dust, it'll ruin the Furnace! So we'll need to Enrich them to get our regular Dust. \\n\\nAnd like usual, Smelt the Dust to get Ingots.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier2_2.png width:250 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.67E7A9A65B14C933.quest_subtitle: "二级矿石处理&7[Tier 2 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.67E7A9A65B14C933.title: "&4粉碎&f并&d富集&f你的&7团块&7[Crush and Enrich our Clumps]&f"
	quest.6B8040401B512E50.quest_desc: ["&3&lC.D.C.&r(&3&l&a化学溶解室&f&r,不是疾病控制与预防中心)是另一种仅用于&l矿石处理&r的&5机器&r.\\n\\n&3&lC.D.C.&r需要&a&a硫酸&f&r和&7矿石&r.\\n\\n&7矿石&r放入&4红色槽&r,而&a&a硫酸&f&r则放入&4红色条&r.\\n\\n完成的&7肮脏矿浆&r会出现在&9蓝色条&r中!\\n&7[The lC.D.C. (lChemical Dissolution Chamber not Center for Disease Control and Prevention) is another Machine only used for lOre Processing. \\n\\nThe lC.D.C. will need Sulfuric Acid and Ore. \\n\\nThe Ore will go in the Red Slot while the Sulfuric Acid will go in the Red Bar. \\n\\nThe finished Dirty Slurry will spawn in the Blue Bar!]&f"]
	quest.6B8040401B512E50.title: "&3&l&a化学溶解室&f&7[lChemical Dissolution Chamber]&f"
	quest.6CD1720B76F47806.quest_desc: ["&2&l生物质发电机&r的工作原理是消耗&2&a生物燃料&f&r,制造&2生物乙醇&r,并用它来产生&a能量&r!\\n\\n不过,这个&2&l发电机&r被严重削弱了,所以建议不要使用它!\\n\\n那是因为你们这些笨蛋总是建造巨大的&a&a西瓜农场&f&r,把服务器的TPS都吃光了!\\n&7[The lBio-Generator works by taking Bio Fuel, making Bioethanol, and using that for Energy! \\n\\nThis lGenerator has been heavily nerfed though, so it is recommened to not use it! \\n\\nThat is because you buttheads keep making massive Melon Farms that eat Servers TPS!]&f"]
	quest.6CD1720B76F47806.title: "&2&l生物质发电机&7[lBio-Generator]&f"
	quest.6DC1E08D019FD543.quest_desc: [
		"我们的&7晶体&r需要更多的&l处理&r!\\n\\n重复之前制造&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r的步骤来制造&e盐水&r.\\n\\n使用一个&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r将&e氯气&f从&e盐水&r中分离出来.\\n\\n然后,将&9水&f放入&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r中获得&7氢气&r.\\n\\n在&a&l&a化学灌注器&f&r中结合&e氯气&f和&7氢气&f,得到&3&a氯化氢&f&r!\\n\\n使用我们的&c&l化学灌注器&r,我们可以用&3&a氯化氢&f&r&c灌注&f&7晶体&f,从每个&7矿石晶体&r中获得 1 个&7矿石碎片&r.\\n&7[Our Crystals will need even more lProcessing! \\n\\nRepeat the previous steps of making a lThermal Evaporation Plant to create Brine. \\n\\nUse an lElectrolytic Separator to Separate the Chlorine from the Brine. \\n\\nThen get Hydrogen from putting Water into an lElectrolytic Separator. \\n\\nCombine the Chlorine and Hydrogen in a lChemical Infuser to get Hydrogen Chloride! \\n\\nWith our lChemical Injector, we can Inject the Crystals with Hydrogen Chloride to get 1 Ore Shard from each Ore Crystal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier4_3.png width:250 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6DC1E08D019FD543.quest_subtitle: "四级矿石处理&7[Tier 4 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.6DC1E08D019FD543.title: "制造更多&3&a氯化氢&f&7[Making more Hydrogen Chloride]&f"
	quest.6F62B5510FA881CD.quest_desc: ["&7锇&r是一种在 Y 轴 56 层以下生成的矿石.它的矿石形状类似于&a绿宝石&r,颜色是&b偏蓝的&7灰色&r!\\n\\n它对于&5&l&d通用机械&f&r中使用的许多&5机器&r都很有用!所以你需要很多!\\n\\n你也可以用它来合成&7盔甲&f和&7工具&r!&7盔甲&f和&7剑&r的护甲值与&c下界合金&r相同!而&7镐&r则与&7&a铁镐&f&r相同.\\n&7[Osmium is an Ore that spawns below Y Level 56. It's Ore is in similar shape to Emerald with the Color being a Blue-ish Grey! \\n\\nIt will be useful for many of the Machines used in lMekanism! So you'll need a lot of it! \\n\\nYou can also Craft Armor and Tools from it! The Armor and Sword are same Points as Netherite! While the Pickaxe is the same as an Iron Pickaxe.]&f"]
	quest.6F62B5510FA881CD.quest_subtitle: "基础合成锭&7[The Base Crafting Ingot]&f"
	quest.6F62B5510FA881CD.title: "&7锇&7[Osmium]&f"
	quest.71869B1D81D6A7EF.quest_desc: ["&2&lP.R.C.&r(&2&l&a加压反应室&f&r)将多种&b流体&f和&c化学品&r与一个&e物品&f结合,制造新的&e物品&f和&c化学品&r!\\n\\n&b流体&r,很可能是&9水&r,放入最左边的条.&c化学品&r放入旁边的条,初始的&e物品&r放入&4红色槽&r.\\n\\n完成的&e物品&r会出现在&9蓝色槽&r中,而完成的&c化学品&r会在&9蓝色条&r中.\\n\\n&2&lP.R.C.&r可以制造一些物品,比如 HDPE 物品、&7火药&r和&a硫&r,甚至&2核物品&r!\\n&7[The lP.R.C. (lPressurized Reaction Chamber) combines multiple Fluids and Chemicals with an Item to make new Items and Chemicals! \\n\\nFluids, most likely Water, go in the farthest Left Bar. Chemicals go in the Bar next to it, and initial Items in the Red Slot. \\n\\nThe finished Item will spawn in the Blue Slot and the finished Chemical will be in the Blue Bar. \\n\\nThe lP.R.C. can make a few Items like HDPE Items, Gunpowder and Sulfur, and even Nuclear Items!]&f"]
	quest.71869B1D81D6A7EF.title: "&2&l&a加压反应室&f&7[lPressurized Reaction Chamber]&f"
	quest.71CF9E59F8F0B4A6.quest_desc: ["这些&5机器&r甚至比&c&l高级&r的还要好!\\n\\n使用&b&l精英&r等级的&e物品&r来制造这些&5机器&r!\\n&7[These Machines are even better than lAdvanced! \\n\\nUse Items from the lElite Tier to make these Machines!]&f"]
	quest.71CF9E59F8F0B4A6.title: "更好的&5机器&r!&7[Even better Machines!]&f"
	quest.7276892E129A739B.quest_desc: ["你以为这就是&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的全部了吗？你甚至毫无头绪!\\n\\n不过,在我们到达那里之前,让我们准备好一些&5机器&f和&a硫&r!\\n\\n我们面前还有很长的路要走.\\n&7[You think this is all lMekanism has? You don't even have a clue! \\n\\nBefore we get there though, let's get some Machines and Sulfur ready! \\n\\nWe're going to have a long road ahead of us.]&f"]
	quest.7276892E129A739B.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f:反应堆&7[lMekanism: Reactors]&f"
	quest.73E6878553BA6908.quest_desc: ["你喜欢抽屉吗？&5&l&d通用机械&f&r给了我们一些!只是这些叫做&e箱子&r.\\n\\n&e箱子&r只能存放一种类型的物品,但可以存放成吨的该&e物品&r!\\n\\n你可以对&e箱子&r使用&3配置器&r,将其设置为自动输出到下方的容器.\\n\\n如果&e箱子&r中有&e物品&f,你可以按住 Shift &a右击&f它来锁定该&e物品&r.\\n\\n&a&l基础&r:可容纳 64 组.\\n\\n&c&l高级&r:可容纳 128 组.\\n\\n&b&l精英&r:可容纳 512 组.\\n\\n&d&l终极&r:可容纳 4,096 组.\\n&7[You like Drawers? lMekanism gives us some! Just these are called Bins. \\n\\nBins can hold only one type of Item but will hold tons of Stacks of that Item! \\n\\nYou can use a Configurator on the Bin to set it to automatically Output to the Inventory below it. \\n\\nIf there is an Item in the Bin, you can Shift Right Click it to Lock that Item. \\n\\nlBasic: holds 64 Stacks. \\n\\nlAdvanced: holds 128 Stacks. \\n\\nlElite: holds 512 Stacks. \\n\\nlUltimate: holds 4,096 Stacks.]&f"]
	quest.73E6878553BA6908.quest_subtitle: "抽屉&7[Drawers]&f"
	quest.73E6878553BA6908.title: "&e箱子&7[Bins]&f"
	quest.74200A48498DD7F8.quest_desc: ["&e&l&a太阳能发电模块&f&r将在&e白天&r暴露在&b天空&r下时产生&a能量&r.\\n\\n这是一个非常简单的自动&e&l发电机&r,只是合成它们很烦人!\\n\\n它们产生的&a能量&r不如&b&l&a风力发电机&f&r多(仅在白天),但能产生更多的爆发能量且占用空间更小!\\n\\n它们已被加强,现在可以存储大约 40kFE!\\n&7[The lSolar Generator will Generate Energy based on being exposed to the Sky during Daytime. \\n\\nIt is a very simple to use automatic lGenerator, just Crafting them is annoying! \\n\\nThey won't generate Energy as much as lWind Generators do (only Daytime) but produce more in Bursts and take up less Space! \\n\\nThey have been buffed and can now hold around 40kFE!]&f"]
	quest.74200A48498DD7F8.quest_subtitle: "约产生 60FE/t&7[Generates about 60FE/t]&f"
	quest.74200A48498DD7F8.title: "&e&l&a太阳能发电模块&f&7[lSolar Generator]&f"
	quest.7485BCBE366501DF.quest_desc: [
		"如果我们想要更多的&7矿石&r!我们需要一种更好的方法来&l处理&r我们的&7矿石&r.氢气不行,让我们试试&3&a氯化氢&f&r.\\n\\n显然,为此我们需要&e氯气&r!\\n\\n查看&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r任务以更详细地了解如何合成多方块结构,但基本上我们需要一个.\\n\\n将&9水&f输入&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r以(缓慢地)制造&e盐水&r.\\n\\n把&e盐水&r扔进&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r,得到&7钠&r和&e氯气&r!&7钠&r对&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r有帮助……但对&l矿石处理&r没用!\\n&7[If we want even more Ores! We'll need a better way of lProcessing our Ores. Hydrogen won't work, let's try Hydrogen Chloride. \\n\\nObviously for that we'll need Chlorine! \\n\\nLook at the lThermal Evaporation Plant Quest to learn in better detail how to Craft the Mutliblock, but basically we'll need one. \\n\\nFeed Water into a lThermal Evaporation Plant to (slowly) make Brine. \\n\\nThrow that Brine into an lElectrolytic Separator to get Sodium and Chlorine! Sodium is helpful for lFission Reactor... but not lOre Processing!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier3_1.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.7485BCBE366501DF.quest_subtitle: "三级矿石处理&7[Tier 3 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.7485BCBE366501DF.title: "制造&e氯气&7[Making Chlorine ]&f"
	quest.75E4751F7A802A44.quest_desc: [
		"多有趣啊!一份&c化学品&r的购物清单!我们是沃尔特·怀特吗？\\n\\n首先,也是最重要的,对于&a&a硫酸&f&r,是&e硫&r!挖一些然后&b氧化&r它得到&e&a二氧化硫&f&r.\\n\\n不过我们还需要一点&b氧气&r,所以让我们用&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r处理&9水&r来获得更多.\\n然后,在&c&l&a化学灌注器&f&r中将新获得的&b氧气&r与&e&a二氧化硫&f&r结合,得到&c&a三氧化硫&f&r.\\n\\n先把那个&e硫&r放一边,等我们得到&a水蒸气&f!要得到&a水蒸气&f,将&9水&r通过&c&l旋转式&b冷凝器&r.\\n&7[How fun! A shopping List of Chemicals! What are we Walter White? \\n\\nFirst, and most important, for Sulfuric Acid, is Sulfur! Mine some then Oxidize it to get Sulfur Dioxide. \\n\\nWe'll need a little more Oxygen though, so let's get some more with an lElectrolytic Separator being fed Water. \\nThen, combine that new-found Oxygen with the Sulfur Dioxide in a lChemical Infuser to get Sulfur Trioxide. \\n\\nLeave that Sulfur whatever for a moment until we get Water Vapor! To get Water Vapor, put Water through a lRotary Condensator. ]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier4_1.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.75E4751F7A802A44.quest_subtitle: "四级矿石处理&7[Tier 4 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.75E4751F7A802A44.title: "制造&a&a硫酸&f&7[Creating Sulfuric Acid]&f"
	quest.763FB27929E053BE.quest_desc: ["&9过滤器&r&8升级&r仅用于&b&l电动泵&r.\\n\\n&b&l泵&r的工作方式相同,但不再是抽取&9水&r,而是抽取&9&a重水&f&r.\\n\\n&9&a重水&f&r将作为&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r的燃料所需!\\n&7[Filter Upgrades are used only in lElectric Pumps. \\n\\nThe lPumps will work the same, but instead of picking up Water, they will pick up Heavy Water. \\n\\nHeavy Water will be needed for Fuel for the lFission Reactor!]&f"]
	quest.763FB27929E053BE.title: "&9过滤器&r&8升级&7[Filter Upgrade]&f"
	quest.7778937DF377C1B4.quest_desc: [
		"这是自动产生&a能量&r的一个绝佳选择.\\n&7[This is a great option for automatically generating Energy.]&f"
		""
		"&b&l&a风力发电机&f&r产生的&a能量&r量基于其 Y 轴高度.\\n&7[The amount of Energy the lWind Generator creates is based on its Y Level.]&f"
		""
		"这大约产生 90FE/t &a与海平面持平&f,最多能产生 360FE/t!\\n&7[This generates around 90FE/t at sea level and the most it can produce is 360FE/t!]&f"
		""
		"&b&l&a风力发电机&f&r也需要上方有&b天空&r才能工作,就像信标一样!\\n&7[The lWind Generator will also need Sky above it to work, like a Beacon!]&f"
	]
	quest.7778937DF377C1B4.quest_subtitle: "从风中产生能量&7[Generates Power from the Wind]&f"
	quest.7778937DF377C1B4.title: "&b&l&a风力发电机&f&7[lWind Generator]&f"
	quest.77FB313845779AED.quest_desc: [
		"现在使用另一个&a&l&a化学灌注器&f&r来&a&l灌注&r我们的&a水蒸气&f和&c&a三氧化硫&f&r.现在我们有了&a&a硫酸&f&r!\\n\\n将&a&a硫酸&f&r用管道输送到&3&l化学溶解室&r中,用&a酸&r&3溶解&r我们的&7矿石&f.这将给我们&7脏矿石浆&r,这是&7矿石&r的&c化学品&r形式.\\n\\n3个&7原矿&r会给出&a2桶&f&7矿石浆&r,1个&7矿石块&r会给出&a1桶&f&7矿石浆&r.\\n\\n我们不能带着&7脏矿石浆&r到处走,这太尴尬了!我们需要清洗它!启动一个&a&l&a化学清洗机&f&r,放入一些&9水&r(和洗衣粉).\\n\\n每1mb的&7脏浆液&r将被转化为1mb的&7矿石浆&r.\\n\\n现在我们的&7浆液&r都干净了,我们可以把它放入&5&l&a化学结晶器&f&r.这将给我们&7矿石晶体&r!是的,不同于&7碎片&f和&7团簇&r.每200mb的&7矿石浆&r等于1个&7晶体&r.\\n&7[Now use another lChemical Infuser to lInfuse our Water Vapor and Sulfur Trioxide. Now we have our Sulfuric Acid! \\n\\nPipe the Sulfuric Acid into a lC.D.C. to Melt down our Ores with Acid. This will give us Dirty Ore Slurry, a Chemical form of Ores. \\n\\n3 Raw Ore will give 2 Buckets of Ore Slurry and 1 Ore Block will give 1 Bucket of Ore Slurry. \\n\\nWe can't go around with Dirty Ore Slurry, it's embarrassing! We'll need to clean it! Start up a lChemical Washer and put some Water (and laundry detergent) into it. \\n\\nEvery 1mb of Dirty Slurry will be turned into 1mb of Ore Slurry. \\n\\nNow that our Slurry is all clean, we can put it into a lChemical Crystallizer. This will give us Ore Crystals! Yes, different from Shards and Clumps. Each 200mb of Ore Slurry is equal to 1 Crystal.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier4_2.png width:300 height:50 align:center}"
	]
	quest.77FB313845779AED.quest_subtitle: "四级矿石处理&7[Tier 4 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.77FB313845779AED.title: "用&a酸&f溶解&7矿石&f并&5结晶&r它们&7[Melting Ores with Acid and Crystallizing them]&f"
	quest.78DD2A3DFF6D1613.quest_desc: ["用2个&2&a生物燃料&f&r,我们可以通过&2&l加压反应室&r制造1个&a基质&r.\\n\\n嗯……我们还需要在&2&l加压反应室&r中加入&9水&r和氢气,然后我们会得到&a基质&r以及&d化学品乙烯&r.\\n\\n为了制造&a高密度聚乙烯丸&f,我们需要&a基质&r,并将&d化学品乙烯&r转化为&d液态乙烯&r.我们可以使用&c&l旋转&b冷凝器&r将其转化为&b液体&r!\\n\\n现在将我们的&d液态乙烯&f和&a基质&r都扔进&2&l加压反应室&r来制造&a高密度聚乙烯丸&f!\\n\\n然后我们可以将4个丸粒合成一个&a高密度聚乙烯棒&f,或者&d富集&r3个丸粒来制造一个&a高密度聚乙烯片&f.\\n&7[With 2 Bio Fuel we can make 1 Substrate through the lP.R.C.. \\n\\nWell... we'll also need Water and Hydrogen in the lP.R.C. but then we'll get our Substrate and also Chemical Ethene. \\n\\nIn order to make HDPE Pellets we'll need our Substrate as well as turning our Chemical Ethene into Liquid Ethene. We can use a lRotary Condensator to turn it Liquid! \\n\\nNow throw both of our Liquid Ethene and Substrates into the lP.R.C. to make HDPE Pellets! \\n\\nWe can then Craft 4 Pellets together to make a HDPE Rod or Enrich 3 of them to make a HDPE Sheet.]&f"]
	quest.78DD2A3DFF6D1613.title: "使用一切将&2&a生物燃料&f&r转化为高密度聚乙烯&7[Using everything to turn Bio Fuel into HDPE]&f"
	quest.7934873E784C4B3C.quest_desc: [
		"这看起来很熟悉？\\n\\n现在我们又有了&7碎片&r.不过,在对它们做任何事情之前,我们需要&b氧气&r.\\n\\n将&9水&f扔进&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r以获得&b氧气&r.然后,用&c管道&r将&b氧气&f从&9&l分离器&r输送到&b&l提纯仓&r.\\n\\n有了&b氧气&f,&b&l提纯仓&r可以将你的&7碎片&f转化为&7矿石团簇&r.\\n\\n现在,&c粉碎&r那些&7团簇&f以获得&7脏粉&r.然后,&d富集&f那些&7脏粉&f以获得&7&a矿石粉&f&r.\\n\\n最后&6烧炼&r那个&7粉&r,以获得我们美丽的&l处理过的矿石&r!\\n&7[This seems familiar? \\n\\nNow we have Shards again. Before we do anything with them though, we'll need Oxygen. \\n\\nThrow Water into an lElectrolytic Separator to get Oxygen. Then, Tube that Oxygen from the lSeparator to the lPurifier. \\n\\nWith that Oxygen, the lPurifier can turn your Shards into Ore Clumps. \\n\\nNow, Crush those Clumps to get Dirty Dust. Then, Enrich those Dirty Dust to get Ore Dust. \\n\\nAnd finally Smelt that Dust, to get our beautifully lProcessed Ore!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_tier3_3.png width:250 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.7934873E784C4B3C.quest_subtitle: "四级矿石处理&7[Tier 4 Ore Processing]&f"
	quest.7934873E784C4B3C.title: "&7晶体&f、&7碎片&f、&7团簇&f,等等&7[Crystal, Shard, Clump, ETC]&f"
	quest.7952DA35B4F5C598.quest_desc: ["一个&7桶&r不够用？一堆&7桶&r也不够用？那么朋友,你需要一些&b&a流体储罐&f&r!\\n\\n&b&a流体储罐&f&r可以容纳多个&7桶&r的同一种&b流体&r,并且可以像&7桶&r一样移动.不过遗憾的是,它们无法放置源方块.\\n\\n要添加或取出&b流体&r,你需要配置&b机械管道&r来进行输入或输出.\\n\\n&a&l基础型&r:可容纳3&a2桶&f流体.\\n\\n&c&l高级型&r:可容纳64桶流体.\\n\\n&b&l精英型&r:可容纳128桶流体.\\n\\n&d&l终极型&r:可容纳256桶流体.\\n&7[What a Bucket isn't enough? A Stack of Buckets isn't enough either? Then friend, you'll need some Fluid Tanks! \\n\\nFluid Tanks can hold multiple Buckets of one Fluid within them and can then be moved around like a Bucket. These unfortunately can not place Source Blocks though. \\n\\nTo add or take out Fluid, you'll need Mechanical Pipes configured to do either or. \\n\\nlBasic: will hold 32 Buckets of Fluids. \\n\\nlAdvanced: will hold 64 Buckets of Fluids. \\n\\nlElite: will hold 128 Buckets of Fluid. \\n\\nlUltimate: will hold 256 Buckets.]&f"]
	quest.7952DA35B4F5C598.title: "&b&a流体储罐&f&7[Fluid Tanks]&f"
	quest.7AE502EDB73BD57A.quest_desc: ["&4&l粉碎机&r,顾名思义!就像其他模组的&4粉碎机&r一样……\\n\\n我们可以从锭中获得粉末,从&7石头&r中获得&7圆石&r,从&2植物&r中获得&2&a生物燃料&f&r!\\n\\n许多配方都需要粉末,所以你肯定需要它.尤其是制作&8升级组件&r!\\n&7[The lCrusher does as the name suggests! Just like every other Mod's Crushers... \\n\\nWe can get Dust from Ingots, Cobble from Stone, and Bio Fuel from Plants! \\n\\nDust will be needed for lots of Recipes so you'll definitely need this. Especially for making Upgrades!]&f"]
	quest.7AE502EDB73BD57A.quest_subtitle: "它能粉碎东西.&7[It Crushes Things.]&f"
	quest.7AE502EDB73BD57A.title: "&4&l粉碎机&7[lCrusher]&f"
	quest.7B0DFA55B4D8B16D.quest_desc: [
		"&a&l传送器&r将允许我们在任何维度传送到任何地方,只要&5机器&r被制造出来并且&a供能&r!\\n\\n那么,我们如何制造它并为它供能呢？\\n\\n首先,要制造&a&l传送器&r,我们需要1个&a传送器方块&f和9个&a&a传送框架&f&r.\\n\\n&a传送器方块&r是&a&l传送器&r的主要&a控制器&r.它是需要&a能量&r的方块,一旦&a供能&r,我们就可以打开它.在这里,我们可以设置一个类似于&5&a量子传送装置&f&r的网络,输入一个名称并点击勾选按钮来创建网络!\\n\\n现在,当其他&a&l传送器结构&r或&a传送器方块&r被设置到该网络时(通过在其GUI中点击已命名的网络),你可以使用&a&l传送器&r传送到同一网络中的其他&a&l传送器&r.\\n\\n现在关于建造&a&l传送器结构&r.在&a传送器方块&r的每一侧放置一个&a&a传送框架&f&r.在这些框架上方再放置3个,使其高度达到4格.在&a传送器方块&r上方留出2格空间,你可以放置最后一个&a&a传送框架&f&r.\\n\\n现在,当供能并设置好后,&a&l传送器&r就准备就绪,你可以穿过生成的任何颜色的传送门!\\n\\n(你可以在&a&l传送器&r的GUI中更改每个传送门的颜色!)\\n&7[lTeleporters will allow us to Teleport anywhere in any Dimension as long as the Machine is made and Powered! \\n\\nNow how do we make it and Power it? \\n\\nFirst, to make the lTeleporter we'll need 1 Teleporter Block and 9 Teleporter Frames. \\n\\nThe Teleporter Block is the main Controller of the lTeleporter. It is the Block that will need Energy, and once Powered we can open it. Here we can set a Network similar to the Quantum Entangloporter, type in a name and click the Checkmark to make the Network! \\n\\nNow when other lTeleporter Structures or Teleporter Blocks, are set to that Network (by clicking the named Network in their GUI) you can use the lTeleporter to obviously Teleport to the other lTeleporters at the same Network. \\n\\nNow about making the lTeleporter Structure. Place a Teleporter Frame on each side of the Teleporter Block. Above those place 3 more to make it 4 Blocks high. With 2 Blocks space above the Teleporter Block, you can place our last Teleporter Frames. \\n\\nNow when Powered and set, the lTeleporter will be ready and you can walk through whatever colored Portal spawned! \\n\\n(You can change the Color for each in the lTeleporter GUI!)]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/meka_portal1.png width:200 height:75 align:center}"
		"放置&a传送器方块&r,并在其旁边放置2个&a&a传送框架&f&r.\\n&7[Place the Teleporter Block with 2 Teleporter Frames next to it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/meka_portal2.png width:150 height:125 align:center}"
		"现在,在之前的框架上放置&a&a传送框架&f&r.\\n&7[Now place Teleporter Frames on the previous ones.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/meka_portal3.png width:100 height:125 align:center}"
		"重复此步骤.\\n&7[Repeat.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/meka_portal4.png width:100 height:140 align:center}"
		"现在,我们需要一整排&a&a传送框架&f&r作为顶部.\\n&7[Now, we'll need a whole row of Teleporter Frames for the top.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/meka_portal5.png width:110 height:150 align:center}"
		"一旦所有设置完成,你选择的传送门应该会像这样出现!\\n&7[Once everything is set, the Portal of your choosing should appear like so!]&f"
	]
	quest.7B0DFA55B4D8B16D.quest_subtitle: "最顶级的传送技术&7[Teleportation at its Finest]&f"
	quest.7B0DFA55B4D8B16D.title: "&a自定义传送门&f!&7[Custom Portals!]&f"
	quest.7C687DCF71D77761.quest_desc: ["&c&l高级型&r是&a&l基础型&r的升级.\\n\\n&c&l高级型&r机器将比&a&l基础级&r容纳更多&e物品&f,移动更多&e物品&r,并拥有更多槽位.\\n\\n&c&l高级型&r由&c&a灌注合金&f&f、&c高级&a电路板&f&f和通常的&7锇&r制成!\\n\\n&c高级&a电路板&f&r由2个&c&a灌注合金&f&r和1个&a基础&a电路板&f&r制成.\\n&7[lAdvanced is the Upgrade to lBasic. \\n\\nlAdvanced Machines will hold more Items, move more Items, and have more Slots than lBasic Tier. \\n\\nlAdvanced are made from Infused Alloys, Advanced Control Circuit, and usually Osmium! \\n\\nAdvanced Control Circuits are made from 2 Infused Alloys and a Basic Control Circuit.]&f"]
	quest.7C687DCF71D77761.title: "&c&l高级级&7[lAdvanced Tier]&f"
	quest.7CC49360D07086B8.quest_desc: ["&o”通过使用高度精细的原子机械,我们可以将所有物质分解到分子水平,并通过特定波长移动这些分子……”&r哦,得了吧,这根本就是魔法!\\n使用2个&5&a量子传送装置&f&r,我们可以无线传输&e物品&f、&b流体&f、&c化学品&f、&6热量&f和&a能量&r!\\n\\n首先,我们需要连接&5&a量子传送装置&f&r.我们通过进入其中一个的文本栏,输入一个网络名称来实现.\\n\\n它可以是数字、字母、符号,随便什么,输入后点击勾选按钮!然后,进入第二个&5&a量子传送装置&f&r,点击已设置的&a网络名称&f.现在它们就连接起来了.\\n\\n之后,将你的&b管道&f、&c导管&f、&a线缆&r等连接到&5&a量子传送装置&f&r,并在另一个装置上放置更多设备甚至&5机器&r.\\n\\n一旦全部准备就绪,更改&a侧面配置&f以实际移动我们的物品.别忘了设置自动弹出!\\n&7[\"Through using highly detailed Atomic Machinery we can take all Matter apart to the molecular level and move those molecules through specific wave lengths...\" Oh come on this is just Magic! \\nWith 2 Quantum Entangloporters we can Wirelessly move Items, Fluids, Chemicals, Heat, and Energy! \\n\\nFirst, we need to connect the Quantum Entangloporters. We do this by going into the Text Bar of one, and typing out a Network name. \\n\\nIt can be Numbers, Letters, Symbols, whatever just Type it and hit the Checkmark Button! Then, go into the second Quantum Entangloporter and Click the name of the Set Network Name. Now they are connected. \\n\\nAfter that, Connect your Pipes, Tubes, Cables whatever, to a Quantum Entangloporter and place more or even a Machine to the other one. \\n\\nOnce that is all ready, change the Side Configs in order to actually move our things around. Don't forget to set Auto-Eject!]&f"]
	quest.7CC49360D07086B8.quest_subtitle: "无线传输能量、气体、流体,一切.&7[Wireless Power, Gases, Fluids, Everything.]&f"
	quest.7CC49360D07086B8.title: "&5&a量子传送装置&f&7[Quantum Entangloporters]&f"
	quest.7ECA0633AF1AEC19.quest_desc: ["&e&l&a精密锯木机&f&r将用于”回收”&6木质物品&r.\\n\\n只需给它一些&a能量&r,扔进一个&6木质物品&r,然后等待!\\n\\n它会把床变成3个&6&a木板&f&r和3个羊毛.把&6门&r变成&6&a木板&f&r.把&2原木&f变成6个&6木板&r,而不是4个!\\n\\n它还会把&7木棍&r变成&6锯末&r,这是制作&6&a纸板箱&f&r所需要的!\\n&7[The lPrecision Sawmill will work to \"recycle\" Wood Items. \\n\\nJust give it some Energy and throw a Wood Item in and wait! \\n\\nIt will turn Beds into 3 Wood Planks and 3 Wool. Doors into Wood Planks. And Logs into 6 Planks instead of 4! \\n\\nIt will also turn Sticks into Sawdust which is needed for the Cardboard Box!]&f"]
	quest.7ECA0633AF1AEC19.title: "&e&l&a精密锯木机&f&7[lPrecision Sawmill]&f"
	task.03C590DB786810FB.title: "能量立方&7[Energy Cubes]&f"
	task.09788D3638E59F3B.title: "等级安装器&7[Tier Installers]&f"
	task.11EF7663818B6CC6.title: "储物箱&7[Bins]&f"
	task.16E5E87F1CAC042A.title: "化学品储罐&7[Chemical Tanks]&f"
	task.2C1B1D314E190B80.title: "个人存储&7[Personal Storage]&f"
	task.36B9FB74D9BF26E4.title: "热力学导体&7[Thermodynamic Conductors]&f"
	task.4558919345C3BE5D.title: "富集机&7[Enrichers]&f"
	task.4632192573FD8501.title: "机械管道&7[Mechanial Pipes]&f"
	task.4B60ACBCC3B46D1D.title: "富集物品&7[Enriched Items]&f"
	task.4B6C5B2099B18AB7.title: "冶炼炉&7[Smelters]&f"
	task.50795B2B2A320D16.title: "加压导管&7[Pressurized Tubes]&f"
	task.564D0E533237E951.title: "净化器&7[Purifiers]&f"
	task.62F11A588B293CA6.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6877D91D6603E4FD.title: "通用线缆&7[Universal Cables]&f"
	task.68C11540A9010775.title: "&a流体储罐&f&7[Fluid Tanks]&f"
	task.6B24D8667BC856A3.title: "物流运输器&7[Logistical Transporters]&f"
	task.6DCF32EB40B8E9C6.title: "&a矿石粉&f&7[Ore Dusts]&f"
	task.729C1974AE346ECA.title: "净化器&7[Purifiers]&f"
	task.770B8B984F85AB73.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.008E65AF545A706E.quest_desc: [
		"虽然是&5&l&d通用机械&f&r中最昂贵的&5机器&r之一,但使用起来其实并不那么困难!\\n\\n首先,建造完成后,我们需要用&a钋&r为其添加燃料.用&c导管&r将一些&a钋&r导入&d&a超临界移相器端口&f&r,因为我们需要将&a钋&r充能成&d反物质&r!\\n\\n要充能,我们需要为&d超导线圈&r供能!用&a线缆&r将&m巨量&r的&a能量&r输入&d&a超临界移相器端口&f&r,以便它们能将其传输到&d超导线圈&r.\\n每个&d超导线圈&r只能承受一定量的&a能量&r,因此为了达到最佳效率,请使用2个!是的,你可以只用1个,但拜托,我们需要的是今年就得到&d反物质&r,而不是明年!\\n\\n一旦我们用&m足够&r数百万FE的能量轰击&a钋&r,我们就会得到&d反物质&r.等等,这是&c化学品&r&d反物质&r？!？我们需要……\\n&7[While being one of the most expensive Machines in lMekanism, it isn't actually that difficult to use! \\n\\nFirst, after Building it, we'll need to Fuel it with Polonium. Tube some into one of the SPS Ports because we'll need to charge our Polonium into Antimatter! \\n\\nTo charge it we'll need to Power our Supercharged Coils! Cable some massive amounts of Energy into the SPS Ports so they can move it to the Supercharged Coils. \\nEach Supercharged Coil can only take so much Energy so for optimal efficiency use 2! Yes, you can use 1 but come on we need Antimatter this year not next year! \\n\\nOnce we've blasted the Polonium with enough millions of FE we'll get our Antimatter. Wait this is Chemical Antimatter?!?! We need...]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps1.png width:100 height:75 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps2.png width:100 height:90 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps3.png width:120 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps4.png width:120 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps5.png width:120 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps6.png width:110 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_sps7.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
	]
	quest.008E65AF545A706E.quest_subtitle: "&d&l超级对撞机&7[lSPS]&f"
	quest.008E65AF545A706E.title: "&d&l超临界&a相移&f器&7[lSuper-Critical Phase Shifter]&f"
	quest.00E19377BAE5DD6A.quest_desc: ["这个为我们的&dMeka工具&r添加了&7剪刀&r功能!\\n\\n它不能与&2农业&7单元&r或&5传送&7单元&r同时使用.\\n&7[This one adds Shears to our Meka-Tool! \\n\\nWe can't use it with the Farming Unit or Teleportation Unit.]&f"]
	quest.00E19377BAE5DD6A.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.00E19377BAE5DD6A.title: "&7&a剪切单元&f&7[Shearing Unit]&f"
	quest.011D8CADA29C9C70.quest_desc: ["&e&aQIO驱动器&f&r决定了&e&l&aQIO驱动器阵列&f&r内的存储容量.\\n\\n它们被放置在&5机器&r的库存中以供使用.最多可以放置12个.\\n\\n&e&aQIO驱动器&f&r容纳&e物品&r,并且它们会自动按顺序填充第一个&e&aQIO驱动器&f&r.\\n\\n每个驱动器都有&e物品存储&r上限和&e物品类型&r上限.&e&aQIO驱动器&f&r越好,你能获得的&e物品&f和&e物品类型&r就越多!\\n\\n&a&aQIO驱动器&f&r:是最基础的,拥有16k物品容量和128种类型.这是唯一一个不需要&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r来合成的.\\n\\n&c&a超密集QIO驱动器&f&r:以及之后的所有驱动器都需要&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r.这个驱动器可容纳128k物品和256种物品类型.\\n\\n&b时间膨胀&aQIO驱动器&f&r:可存储1,048k物品和1,024种物品类型.\\n\\n&d&a超质量QIO驱动器&f&r:需要&d反物质&r来合成,但显然能提供最大的存储容量.允许存储16b物品和8,192种物品类型.\\n&7[QIO Drives determine the Storage within lQIO Drive Arrays. \\n\\nThey are placed within the Machines Inventory in order to be used. You can place up to 12 of them. \\n\\nThe QIO Drives hold the Items and they will automatically fill up the first QIO Drive in order. \\n\\nEach of them have an Item Storage limit and Item Type limit. The better the QIO Drive, the more Items and Item Types you'll get! \\n\\nQIO Drive: is the most basic, having 16k Items and 128 Types. This is the only one not needing a lFission Reactor to Craft. \\n\\nHyper-Dense QIO Drive: and everything after will need the lFission Reactor. This one holds 128k Items and 256 Item Types. \\n\\nTime-Dilating QIO Drive: can store 1,048k Items and 1,024 Item Types. \\n\\nSupermassive QIO Drive: will need Antimatter to Craft but will obviously give the most Storage. Allowing 16b Items and 8,192 Item Types.]&f"]
	quest.011D8CADA29C9C70.title: "&e&aQIO驱动器&f&7[QIO Drives]&f"
	quest.0133DA323E24A455.quest_desc: ["说到替换东西(用&a&a辐射防护模块&f&7单元&r替换&6&a防化服&f&r),让我们也替换掉&e&a潜水呼吸装置&f&r吧!\\n\\n将这个&7模块单元&r添加到我们的&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r后,我们将能够在&9水下&r游泳和呼吸!\\n\\n如果我们的&a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r中装有&c喷气背包&7单元&r,当在&9水中&r时,它会为其提供&7氢气&r.\\n&7[Talking about replacing things (Hazmat Suit with Radiation Shielding Unit) lets replace the Scuba Gear! \\n\\nWith this Module Unit added to our lMekaSuit Helmet, we will be able to swim Underwater and breathe! \\n\\nIf we have a Jetpack Unit in our lMekaSuit Bodyarmor it will feed it Hydrogen when in Water.]&f"]
	quest.0133DA323E24A455.quest_subtitle: "头盔&7[Helmet]&f"
	quest.0133DA323E24A455.title: "&9电解呼吸&7单元&7[Electrolytic Breathing Unit]&f"
	quest.02C6132919DEAF2A.quest_desc: ["在我们开始制造&a能量&r之前,让我们先把蒸汽弄得到处都是.我们可以通过用&9&a分压元件&f&r包围&9&a复杂旋钮装置&f&r来实现!\\n\\n在那层之上,我们需要新的一层,这一层布满&a电磁线圈&r.这些线圈会因为&9&a复杂旋钮装置&f&r而运动,它们彼此之间的运动通过磁力产生&a能量&r.水力发电厂也是同样的原理!\\n\\n在&a电磁线圈&r上方,我们可以使用&9&a饱和冷凝器&f&r,它将把我们的蒸汽回收成一些&9水&r!&9水&r将通过&9通风口&r被抽出.\\n&7[Before we start making Energy let's get our Steam all over the place. We can do that by surrounding the Rotational Complex with Pressure Dispersers! \\n\\nAbove that layer we'll need a new layer, this one full of Electromagnetic Coils. These will be moved because of the Rotational Complex, them moving with each other is what develops Energy through their Magnetic Forces. Same thing happens with Hydroelectric Plants! \\n\\nAbove the Electromagnetic Coils we can use Saturating Condensers which will recycle our Steam back into some Water! The Water will be extracted through the Vents.]&f"]
	quest.02C6132919DEAF2A.title: "用&9&l涡轮机&r制造&a能量&r&7[Making Energy with a lTurbine]&f"
	quest.0306D25C7407FE88.quest_desc: ["要实际启动&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r,我们需要的另一个部分是&6热量&r!我们可以使用&4激光&r或通过&c导管&r导入&6热量&r.\\n\\n我们这里就只用&4激光&r.更具体地说,是&4&a激光增幅器&f&r向&c&a激光聚焦矩阵&f&r发射一定量的能量.\\n\\n我们需要一个拥有1GFE&a能量&r的&4&a激光增幅器&f&r向&c&a激光聚焦矩阵&f&r发射.这听起来需要很多&a能量&r,但别担心,我们会收回成本的!\\n\\n按照&4&a激光增幅器&f&r任务,我们需要向&4&a激光增幅器&f&r发射&4激光&r.但每个激光器每几秒只能提供大约1MFE……\\n\\n与其等上一年,我们可以使用多个&4激光&r射向多个&4&a激光增幅器&f&r,而这些增幅器再射向那个瞄准&c&a激光聚焦矩阵&f&r的增幅器.\\n\\n放置&4&a激光增幅器&f&r,使它们一个接一个地排列,同时每个增幅器都有4个&4激光&r从其他方向射向它!\\n&7[Another part we'll need to actually start the lFusion Reactor is Heat! We can use either Lasers or Porting Heat into it. \\n\\nWe're just going to use Lasers here. More specifically Laser Amplifier shooting a certain amount into the Laser Focus Matrix. \\n\\nWe'll need a Laser Amplifier with 1GFE worth of Energy to be shot into the Laser Focus Matrix. It sounds like a lot of Energy but don't worry we'll get it back! \\n\\nFollowing the Laser Amplifier Quest, we'll need to shoot Lasers into the Laser Amplifier. But each only gives about 1MFE every few seconds... \\n\\nInstead of waiting a year, we can use multiple Lasers shooting into multiple Laser Amplifiers that shoot into the one targeting the Laser Focus Matrix. \\n\\nPlace the Laser Amplifiers so that they have another behind each other, while all of them have 4 Lasers shooting from the other directions!]&f"]
	quest.0306D25C7407FE88.title: "&c&a激光聚焦矩阵&f&7[Laser Focus Matrix]&f"
	quest.03840E4C74731E0C.quest_desc: ["听着,我一直在告诉你们在大多数&5&l&d通用机械&f&r任务中使用&9电动泵&r.\\n\\n但说实话,我得让你们毕业了.&2&l反应堆&r将需要更多&9水&r,所以我授予你们,&9无限水源&r!\\n\\n&9无限水源&r拥有无限的&9水&r,并且几乎可以被任何模组的&b管道&r抽出.我推荐使用&9&lID&r(如果可用的话),因为它每游戏刻可以抽出超过20亿mB的&9水&r!\\n\\n我一直使用&9电动泵&r的原因不是我不信任你们用&9无限水源&r,而是因为这些原因:1. 它适用于没有&9无限水源&r的整合包；2. 它来自&5&l&d通用机械&f&r.\\n&7[Listen, I have been telling you guys to use Electric Pumps for most of the lMekanism Quests. \\n\\nBut to be honest I have to let you guys graduate. The lReactors will need more Water so I grant you, the Sink! \\n\\nThe Sink has Infinite Water and can be Piped out from practically any Mod. I recommend using lID if available because it can pull over 2 Billion mB of Water each Tick! \\n\\nThe reason I have been using the Electric Pumps is not because I don't trust you with Sinks rather it is for these reasons. 1. it will stay for Modpacks that don't have Sinks and 2. it is from lMekanism. ]&f"]
	quest.03840E4C74731E0C.title: "&9水&b冷却剂&7[Water Coolant]&f"
	quest.05DA7F48E2A1B77F.quest_desc: ["认识一下&a&l罗比特&r!他是你的新机器人伙伴!\\n\\n将他放置在一个&a充电板&r上以将其设为他家!这很重要,因为&a&l罗比特&r需要&a能量&r来移动和工作.他可以储存40kFE.\\n\\n我们可以&a右击&f他来打开他的图形界面(当然要经过他的允许!).在中间,我们会看到一个屏幕,告诉我们关于他的信息:他的名字、他的&a能量&r、他的工作和他的主人!\\n\\n左边有一些按钮.按&a上天入地&f的顺序:&a传送回家&f会将他带回他的&a充电板&r,重命名会改变他的生物名称,外观是装饰性的&a&l罗比特&r内容!\\n\\n&a能量槽位&r下方是设置他工作的按钮.拾取:将允许&a&l罗比特&r拾取地上的&e物品&r并将其放入他的物品栏.跟随:将使&a&l罗比特&r跟随你或停留在原地.\\n\\n在最右边,还有更多按钮!第一个按钮将调出&a&l罗比特&r主菜单.合成将在&a&l罗比特&r内打开一个合成台!物品栏将打开&a&l罗比特&r的物品栏.在这里你可以存储&e物品&r,或者拾取的&e物品&r会放在这里.烧炼将使用&a能量&r像熔炉一样烧炼&e物品&r.修复将允许你结合两个&e物品&r来修复它们的耐久度.\\n&7[Meet lRobit! He is your new Robotic Companion! \\n\\nPlace him down onto a Chargepad to set it as his Home! This is important as lRobit needs Energy to move and work. He can hold 40kFE. \\n\\nWe can Right Click him to open his GUI (with his permission of course!). In the middle we'll see a Screen that teaches us facts about him: his Name, his Energy, his Job, and his Owner! \\n\\nOn the left we got some Buttons. In order from Top to Bottom: Teleport Home will bring him to his Chargepad, Rename changes his Mob Name, and Appearance is cosmetic lRobit stuff! \\n\\nBelow the Energy Slot is Buttons to set his Job. Pickup: will allow lRobit to pick up Items on the ground and put them in his Inventory. Follow: will make lRobit either Follow you or stop where he is at. \\n\\nTo the far right, is even more Buttons! The first, will bring up the main lRobit menu. Crafting will open up a Crafting Table within lRobit! Inventory will open up lRobit's Inventory. Here you can store Items or where picked up Items will go. Smelting will use Energy to Smelt Items like a Furnace. Repairing will allow you to combine two Items to Repair their Durability.]&f"]
	quest.05DA7F48E2A1B77F.title: "&a&l罗比特&7[lRobit]&f"
	quest.066F78936C8F943B.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r创作,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&e版权所有&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.078B69E9362A5496.quest_desc: ["是的,&5&l&d通用机械&f&r就是这么大!\\n\\n如果你想要你的&2&l反应堆&r和无敌盔甲,那么你来对地方了!\\n\\n首先,我们需要一个&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r,而它需要&2&a裂变燃料&f&r.要制作&2&a裂变燃料&f&r,我们需要一些&c三氧化硫&r.\\n\\n首先将&e硫磺&r放入&c&l化学氧化机&r中制造&e&a二氧化硫&f&r.\\n\\n然后,通过&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r处理&9水&r来制造一些&b氧气&r.\\n\\n现在我们可以将&b氧气&r和&e&a二氧化硫&f&r通过&c&l&a化学灌注器&f&r管道化,来制造我们的&c&a三氧化硫&f&r.\\n&7[Yes, lMekanism is that big! \\n\\nIf you want your lReactors and Invincible Armor, then you are in the right spot! \\n\\nFirst, we'll need a lFission Reactor and that needs Fissile Fuel. To make Fissile Fuel we'll need some Sulfuric Trioxide. \\n\\nStart by putting Sulfur into a lChemical Oxidizier to make Sulfur Dioxide. \\n\\nThen, make some Oxygen by processing Water through an lElectrolytic Separator. \\n\\nNow we can Tube that Oxygen and Sulfur Dioxide into a lChemical Infuser to make our Sulfur Trioxide.]&f"]
	quest.078B69E9362A5496.title: "&5&l&d通用机械&f:反应堆&7[lMekanism: Reactors]&f"
	quest.09D7D3CF61E156B1.quest_desc: ["&2&a裂变燃料组件&f&r构成了&2&a裂变燃料&f&r的存储单元.它们也有助于确定效率.\\n\\n&2裂变燃料组件&r需要放置在&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r中才能工作.\\n\\n它们可以&a堆叠&f在彼此的上方和旁边,但每一堆都需要一个……\\n\\n&2&a控制棒组件&f&r放在它们上面!&2&a控制棒组件&f&r不会改变像&a效率&f这样的东西,但如果&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r内没有&2&a控制棒组件&f&r在它们上方,&2&a裂变燃料组件&f&r将无法工作!\\n&7[Fission Fuel Assembly are what make up the storage for Fissile Fuel. They also help determine Efficiency. \\n\\nFission Fuel Assemblies will need to be placed in the lFission Reactor in order to work. \\n\\nThey can be stacked on top and next to each other, but each stack will need a... \\n\\nControl Rod Assembly on top of them! Control Rod Assembly don't change anything like Efficiency but the Fission Fuel Assembly won't work if there isn't a Control Rod Assembly above them within the lFission Reactor!]&f"]
	quest.09D7D3CF61E156B1.title: "&2&a裂变燃料&f&r的存储与使用&7[Fissile Fuel storage and usage]&f"
	quest.0EBE20E44A7AEC7E.quest_desc: ["这些&7单元&r会让你的双脚乃至整个腿部变得更长更强壮!\\n\\n你可以冲刺跳得更高,走上更高的台阶.\\n\\n安装更多&7单元&r后,你可以跳得更高、跨步更远,并且可以调整&7单元&r的配置来达到更高的高度!\\n&7[These Units will make your Feet and pretty much entire Legs, longer and stronger! \\n\\nYou can Sprint Jump higher and walk up higher steps. \\n\\nYou can Jump and step higher with more Units Installed and you can change the Configs of the Unit to go even higher!]&f"]
	quest.0EBE20E44A7AEC7E.quest_subtitle: "靴子&7[Boots]&f"
	quest.0EBE20E44A7AEC7E.title: "&e液压推进&7单元&7[Hydraulic Propulsion Unit]&f"
	quest.0F97EFAFD6E68F8D.quest_desc: ["有了这个&7单元&r,&dMeka工具&r挖掘方块的速度会快得多!\\n\\n安装得越多,速度就越快!\\n就像&a效率&f附魔一样.\\n&7[With this Unit the Meka-Tool will Mine Blocks much quicker! \\n\\nThe more you have, the quicker it goes! \\nJust like the Efficiency Enchantment.]&f"]
	quest.0F97EFAFD6E68F8D.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.0F97EFAFD6E68F8D.title: "&e挖掘增效&7单元&7[Excavation Escalation Unit]&f"
	quest.123C0417D85B9DB2.quest_desc: ["&e太阳能充能&7单元&r安装在&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r中,可以为&a&lMekaSuit&r充能!\\n\\n安装得越多,产生的FE就越多.\\n\\n是的,它的工作原理就像普通的&e&a太阳能发电模块&f&r一样……需要&e白天&r并暴露在&b天空&r下!\\n&7[Solar Recharging Units go into lMekaSuit Helmets and will charge the lMekaSuit! \\n\\nThe more you have added, the more FE will be generated. \\n\\nYes, it works just like a normal Solar Generator... Daytime and exposed to the Sky!]&f"]
	quest.123C0417D85B9DB2.quest_subtitle: "头盔&7[Helmet]&f"
	quest.123C0417D85B9DB2.title: "&e太阳能充能&7单元&7[Solar Recharging Unit]&f"
	quest.13A5748DF69D832E.quest_desc: ["&e&l&aQIO驱动器阵列&f&r本身作用不大,我们需要添加一个&e&aQIO仪表板&f&r!\\n\\n&e&l&aQIO仪表板&f&r,像所有与&e&lQIO&r相关的&e物品&r一样,需要设置为同一网络.\\n\\n当最终准备就绪后,我们就可以将&e物品&r存入并访问我们的&e&lQIO系统&r.\\n\\n我们从最重要的部分开始!中间的槽位是存放和取出&e物品&r的地方.我们可以使用左侧的按钮来增加或减少显示的行数,从而增加槽位数量.从2行到7行.\\n\\n槽位上方是&a搜索栏&f,可以查找&e物品&r名称、标签和模组.槽位下方是排序选项.可以按物品名称从A到Z排序,或按堆叠数量从少到多排序.\\n\\n右侧按钮可以设置当我们打开&e&aQIO仪表板&f&r时,输入焦点是&lEMI&r还是&e&lQIO&r的输入栏.\\n\\n现在介绍&e&lQIO系统&r的另一个有用功能:合成!左侧有一个合成按钮!这会打开最多3个合成窗口.每个窗口都有一个我们可以使用的3x3合成网格.\\n\\n合成按钮下方的&a按钮&f会影响从我们物品栏中Shift点击&e物品&r的行为.要么将它们发送到打开的合成窗口,要么发送到&e&lQIO系统&r中.\\n\\n最后一个按钮与&lEMI&r配合使用,用于自动设置配方.被替换的方块要么会放入你的物品栏,要么会放回&e&lQIO系统&r.\\n&7[The lQIO Drive Array doesn't do much on its own, instead we'll need to add a QIO Dashboard! \\n\\nThe lQIO Dashboard, like all Items lQIO related, needs to be set to the same Network. \\n\\nWhen it is finally ready we can deposit and access Items into our lQIO System. \\n\\nWe'll start with the most important parts! The Slots in the middle are where Items can be put, stored, and taken from. We can increase how many Slots are shown with the Buttons on the Left to Increase or Decrease Height. From 2 Rows, to 7. \\n\\nAbove the Slots is the Search Bar to look up Item names, Tags, and Mods. Below the Slots is a Sorting option. Whether Items are A to Z or from least to most Items in a stack. \\n\\nThe Right Button will make it so either when we open the QIO Dashboard, our Typing will start at lEMI or the lQIO Type Bar. \\n\\nNow for another helpful part of the lQIO System, Crafting! On the Left we have a Crafting Button! This will bring up, up to 3 Crafting Windows. These each have a 3x3 Crafting Grid we can use. \\n\\nThe Button below the Crafting Button effects Shift Clicking Items from our Inventory. Either it will send them to the open Crafting Window, or into the lQIO System. \\n\\nThe last Button is used with lEMI and automatically setting up Recipes. Either the replaced Blocks will be put in your Inventory, or back into the lQIO System.]&f"]
	quest.13A5748DF69D832E.title: "&e&aQIO仪表板&f&7[QIO Dashboard]&f"
	quest.141D68BAD039784B.quest_desc: ["我们的&6&l&a热力锅炉&f&r可以用来获取&6&a过热钠&f&r和&9水&r,并将其回收成钠和蒸汽!\\n\\n但是我们如何将&6&a过热钠&f&r和&9水&r送入&6&l锅炉&r呢？\\n\\n使用&6锅炉端口&r!不过我们需要用&3配置器&r来改变&6端口&r的配置.\\n\\n我们的&6&a过热钠&f&r和&9水&r将通过输入&6端口&r添加(使用独立的输入&6端口&r).\\n\\n冷却后的钠将通过输出&6端口&r取出.而蒸汽则有它专用的蒸汽输出&6端口&r!\\n&7[Our lThermoelectric Boiler can be used to get Superheated Sodium and Water and recycle it into Sodium and Steam! \\n\\nBut how do we get our Superheated Sodium and Water into the lBoiler? \\n\\nWith Boiler Ports! We'll need to use a Configurator on them to change the Ports configs though. \\n\\nOur Superheated Sodium and Water will be added in through Input Ports (separate Input Ports). \\n\\nThe cooled down Sodium, will be taken out through an Output Port. And Steam gets its very own Steam Output Port!]&f"]
	quest.141D68BAD039784B.title: "&6锅炉端口&7[Boiler Ports]&f"
	quest.14385D3D359224BC.quest_desc: ["&dMeka工具&r是&5&l&d通用机械&f&r提供的最佳工具,名副其实!\\n\\n它能做&b原子&c拆解器&r能做的一切,而且更好!在破坏方块方面,拥有更高的&a伤害&f和&a攻击速度&f.\\n\\n不过,它没有模式,而是可以使用改装单元!查看它们各自的任务.\\n\\n尽管它使用&3配置器&r来合成,但并不会以任何方式复制它.\\n&7[The Meka-Tool is the best Tool lMekanism offers, hence the name! \\n\\nIt can do everything the Atomic Disassembler just better! Breaking Blocks wise, with more Damage and Attack Speed. \\n\\nInstead of having Modes though, it can use Modification Units! Check out their own Quests. \\n\\nEven though it uses the Configurator to Craft, it doesn't replicate it any way.]&f"]
	quest.14385D3D359224BC.title: "&dMeka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.16DDAE318535D0F9.quest_desc: ["&b原子&c拆解器&r是&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的万能工具!\\n\\n它可以挖掘任何&6AllTheModium万能工具&r能挖的方块!它也可以用作剑……嗯,更像斧头,没有&a横扫&f效果.\\n\\n它有不同的模式,每种模式的&a效率&f和&a能量&r消耗都不同.我们可以通过按住Shift并滚动来切换模式.\\n\\n普通模式:是默认模式.&a效率&f为20,大约相当于&a效率&f II.\\n\\n慢速模式:就像没有效率附魔的万能工具,但使用时消耗的&a能量&r更少!\\n\\n快速模式:消耗多得多的&a能量&r,但速度快得多!就像&a效率&f V.\\n\\n关闭模式:不会破坏方块,其唯一目的是杀戮!\\n&7[The Atomic Disassembler is lMekanism's Paxel! \\n\\nIt can Mine any Blocks an AllTheModium Paxel can! It can also be used as a Sword... well more like an Axe, there's no Sweeping Edge. \\n\\nIt has different Modes, each doing different Efficiency and Energy usage. We can change it by holding Shift and Scrolling. \\n\\nNormal: is default Mode. With an Efficiency of 20 which means just around Efficiency II. \\n\\nSlow: is like a Paxel without Efficiency, but will use less Energy on use! \\n\\nFast: uses a ton more Energy but much faster! Like Efficiency V. \\n\\nOff: will not break Blocks, instead it's sole purpose is to KILL!]&f"]
	quest.16DDAE318535D0F9.title: "&b原子&c拆解器&7[Atomic Disassembler]&f"
	quest.17E2C05C48B03043.quest_desc: ["钠可以作为&b冷却剂&r代替&9水&r.钠效率更高,能达到更高的&6温度&r,但更难获取和重复利用.\\n\\n那么,我们如何获取它呢？\\n\\n我们需要一个&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r.我已经做了大约3个任务来解释如何建造和使用它们,这不会是第4个.\\n\\n我们将使用&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r来处理&9水&r,制造&e盐水&r.\\n\\n然后,我们可以使用一个&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r来分解&e盐水&r,得到我们的钠!\\n\\n还会产生另一种&c化学品&r,但我们不关心它!\\n&7[Sodium can be used as a Coolant instead of Water. Sodium is more Efficient, gets higher Temperatures, but is harder to get and reuse. \\n\\nNow how do we get it? \\n\\nWe'll need a lThermal Evaporation Plant. I've made like 3 Quests explaining how to Build and use them, this won't be the 4th. \\n\\nWe'll use the lThermal Evaporation Plant to take our Water and make Brine. \\n\\nThen, we can use an lElectrolytic Separator to demolish that Brine to get our Sodium! \\n\\nAnd another Chemical but we don't care about it!]&f"]
	quest.17E2C05C48B03043.title: "钠&b冷却剂&7[Sodium Coolant]&f"
	quest.18EB2170CAC48E99.quest_desc: ["&5传送&7单元&r是一个非常独特的&7单元&r.\\n\\n在我们的&dMeka工具&r上添加&5传送&r功能后,我们可以看着一个方块并&a右击&f传送到它上面.\\n\\n它消耗&a能量&r并且有距离限制,但别担心,距离仍然相当远!\\n\\n这个&7单元&r不能与&2农业&7单元&r或&7&a剪切单元&f&r同时工作.\\n&7[Teleportation Unit is a pretty unique Unit. \\n\\nWith our Meka-Tool with Teleportation added we can look at a Block and Right Click to Teleport on to it. \\n\\nIt uses Energy and has a limited range, but don't worry the range is still pretty far! \\n\\nThis Unit can't work with the Farming Unit or Shearing Unit.]&f"]
	quest.18EB2170CAC48E99.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.18EB2170CAC48E99.title: "&5传送&7单元&7[Teleportation Unit]&f"
	quest.1C87535D3CDCDA5F.quest_desc: ["&4&a激光增幅器&f&r有自己的内部&a能量&r存储,但它们不像大多数&5机器&r那样充电.\\n\\n&4&a激光增幅器&f&r的工作方式是通过吸收其他射向它的&4激光&r的电荷来充电!\\n\\n无论是其他&4&a激光增幅器&f&f还是&4激光&r,这就是它们获取&a能量&r的方式.\\n\\n然后,它们会利用这些&a能量&r,根据你在其GUI中设置的配置(延迟、最小值和最大值)发射出更聚焦的光束.\\n\\n延迟是指在达到最小&a能量&r后,等待多少游戏刻才发射.最少的刻数是0,最多是9,999!\\n\\n最小值是指它在发射更强大的&4激光&r之前会储存的&a能量&r量.它等待的最小FE是800mFE,最大是2GFE.\\n\\n最大值的工作原理类似,是指它在发射&4激光&r前会储存的最大能量.\\n&7[Laser Amplifiers have their own Internal Energy Storage, but they don't charge like most Machines. \\n\\nThe way Laser Amplifiers work is by taking Charge from other Lasers shooting into them! \\n\\nWhether it be other Laser Amplifiers or Lasers, that is how they gain Energy. \\n\\nThey will then use that Energy into a more focused beam by the Configs you set within its GUI. Delay, Minimum, and Maximum. \\n\\nDelay is how many Ticks it will wait after reaching the Minimum Eergy to shoot it. The least amount of Ticks is 0 and the most is 9,999! \\n\\nMinimum is the amount of Energy it will hold before shooting an even more powerful Laser! The least FE it will wait for is 800mFE while the most is 2GFE. \\n\\nMaximum works similar with how much it will hold before shooting the Laser. ]&f"]
	quest.1C87535D3CDCDA5F.title: "&4激光增幅&7[Laser Amplifying]&f"
	quest.1FC88A3BFCE6C9D7.quest_desc: ["这个就是&a迅捷潜行&f附魔……只不过现在是个&7单元&r了!\\n&7[This one is just Swift Sneaking Enchantment... just a Unit now!]&f"]
	quest.1FC88A3BFCE6C9D7.quest_subtitle: "护腿&7[Pants]&f"
	quest.1FC88A3BFCE6C9D7.title: "&8机动伺服&7单元&7[Motorized Servo Unit]&f"
	quest.20054D077AFE3F56.quest_desc: ["我们有了&3钚&r,剩下的应该是我们已经有的东西!\\n\\n一个&2&lP.R.C.&r、&9水&r和&d&a氟石粉&f&r!\\n\\n将1,000mB &9水&r、1,000mB &3钚&r和1个&d&a氟石粉&f&r结合,制成1个&3&a钚靶丸&f&r和1,000mB &8乏&a核废料&f&r.\\n\\n&d&a氟石粉&f&r可以像任何&a金属粉末&f一样制作:使用&4&l粉碎机&r、&d&l&a富集仓&f&r,甚至矿石锤!\\n&7[We got our Plutonium and the rest is what we should already have! \\n\\nA lP.R.C., Water, and Fluorite Dust! \\n\\nCombine 1,000mB Water, with 1,000mB Plutonium, and 1 Fluorite Dust to make 1 Plutonium Pellet and 1,000mB Spent Nuclear Waste. \\n\\nFluorite Dust can be made like any Metal Dust: lCrusher, lEnrichment Chamber, or even an Ore Hammer!]&f"]
	quest.20054D077AFE3F56.title: "&3&a钚靶丸&f&7[Plutonium Pellets]&f"
	quest.22171982D22CE15F.quest_desc: ["现在,每个&a&lMekaSuit部件&r不再拥有各自独立的充能,而是共享一个充能池.\\n\\n这对于保持每个&a&l部件&r的充能状态很重要.\\n\\n而这对你的生存至关重要!\\n&7[Instead of each lMekaSuit Part having their own individual Charge, they will now share one Charge. \\n\\nThis is important in keeping every lPart Charged. \\n\\nAnd that is important to keeping you alive!]&f"]
	quest.22171982D22CE15F.quest_subtitle: "胸甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.22171982D22CE15F.title: "&a充能分配&7单元&7[Charge Distribution Units]&f"
	quest.23B68F19A04AF5D7.quest_desc: ["许多这些&a&l&aMekaSuit裤子&f&r的&7单元&r工作原理就像附魔一样.\\n\\n这个单元是二合一!同时包含&a空中速掘&f和&a水亲和模块&f.\\n\\n当你游泳、飞行或坠落时,将不再有挖掘惩罚.\\n&7[Lots of these lMekaSuit Pants Units work just like Enchantments. \\n\\nThis one is a 2 for 1! Both Air Affinity and Aqua Affinity. \\n\\nYou will no longer have a Mining penalty when Swimming or Flying or Falling.]&f"]
	quest.23B68F19A04AF5D7.quest_subtitle: "护腿&7[Pants]&f"
	quest.23B68F19A04AF5D7.title: "陀螺仪稳定&7单元&7[Gyroscopic Stabilization Unit]&f"
	quest.24E800EEC2CAD626.quest_desc: ["&2盖革&7单元&r的工作方式类似于&a剂量计&7单元&r,但它检测的不是你体内的&a辐射&r,而是你周围的&a辐射&r!\\n\\n这样你就能找到它可能隐藏的地方.\\n\\n你还可以启用和禁用它!\\n&7[The Geiger Unit will work like the Dosimeter Unit but instead of Radiation in you, it's Radiation around you! \\n\\nJust so you can find where it might be hiding. \\n\\nYou can also enable and disable it!]&f"]
	quest.24E800EEC2CAD626.quest_subtitle: "胸甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.24E800EEC2CAD626.title: "&2盖革&7单元&7[Geiger Unit]&f"
	quest.27195E9A3482C158.quest_desc: ["&b呼吸净化&7单元&r实际上有几个功能.\\n\\n1. 它会消耗&a能量&r来阻挡&a魔法伤害&f.比如瞬间伤害药水!\\n\\n2. 可以配置为根据药水效果的有益或有害程度来阻挡&a药水效果&f.分为有益、中性和有害.\\n\\n有益效果会以任何方式帮助玩家.比如再生、治疗、速度和力量.中性效果作用不大,比如发光.有害效果会使游戏对玩家来说更困难.比如凋零、虚弱或失明.\\n&7[The Inhalation Purification Unit actually does a few things. \\n\\n1. It will use Energy to block out Magic Damage. Like Potions of Instant Harming! \\n\\n2. It can be Configured to block Potion Effects based on their level of help or harm. Beneficial, Neutral, and Harmful. \\n\\nBeneficial will help the Player in any way. Like Regeneration, Healing, Speed, and Strength. Neutral doesn't do much, like Glowing. Harmful will make the Game harder for the Player. Like Wither, Weakness, or Blindness.]&f"]
	quest.27195E9A3482C158.quest_subtitle: "头盔&7[Helmet]&f"
	quest.27195E9A3482C158.title: "&b呼吸净化&7单元&7[Inhalation Purification Unit]&f"
	quest.2747AEE1F7F97848.quest_desc: ["药水不错,但你不讨厌它们有时间限制吗？\\n\\n不,别提灌注塔!\\n\\n有了这个&7单元&r,你会跑得更快,跳得更高!(但你还是打不好篮球).\\n\\n安装得越多,你就跑得越快,跳得越高!\\n&7[Potions are nice but don't you hate that they have time limits? \\n\\nNo, shut up about the Infusion Pylon! \\n\\nWith this Unit you will run faster and jump higher! (But you're still no good at Basketball). \\n\\nThe more you have, the faster and higher you'll go!]&f"]
	quest.2747AEE1F7F97848.quest_subtitle: "护腿&7[Pants]&f"
	quest.2747AEE1F7F97848.title: "&e运动助推&7单元&7[Locomotive Boosting Unit]&f"
	quest.298A7BED5C2C7582.quest_desc: ["&a感应电容&r放置在&a&l充能&a输导矩阵&f&r内,会增加其存储容量.\\n\\n是的,它们的容量会相互叠加!\\n\\n&a基础感应电容&r:每个可存储3.2GFE.\\n\\n&c高级感应电容&r:每个可存储25.6GFE.\\n\\n&b&a精英输导元件&f&r:每个可存储204.8GFE.\\n\\n&5&a终极输导元件&f&r:每个可存储1.6TFE.\\n&7[Induction Cells are placed within the lEnergized Induction Matrix and will increase the amount of storage it has. \\n\\nAnd yes, their totals will stack on each other! \\n\\nBasic Induction Cell: will hold 3.2GFE each. \\n\\nAdvanced Induction Cells: will hold 25.6GFE each. \\n\\nElite Induction Cell: will hold 204.8GFE each. \\n\\nUltimate Induction Cell: will hold 1.6TFE each.]&f"]
	quest.298A7BED5C2C7582.quest_subtitle: "存储&7[Storage]&f"
	quest.298A7BED5C2C7582.title: "&a感应电容&7[Induction Cells]&f"
	quest.2DC4446A644A4079.quest_desc: ["&6&a防化服&f&r是防止&a辐射&r杀死你的唯一方法.\\n\\n你需要穿戴全套才能防止&a&a辐射中毒&f&r!\\n\\n&a辐射&r会杀死附近的其他生物和玩家,玩家可以通过&6&a防化服&f&r得救……但生物就没那么幸运了!\\n&7[The Hazmat Suit is the only way of preventing Radiation from killing you. \\n\\nYou need to wear the entire set to prevent Radiation Poisoning! \\n\\nRadiation will kill other Mobs and Players near it, the Players can be saved with Hazmat Suits... but Mobs aren't so lucky!]&f"]
	quest.2DC4446A644A4079.title: "&6&a防化服&f&7[Hazmat Suit]&f"
	quest.302E9BC711779A4A.quest_desc: ["让我们暂时放下&e硫磺&r和酸,专注于&2&a裂变燃料&f&r的&2放射性&r部分!\\n\\n现在让我们看看……什么是&2放射性&r、储量丰富,并且在&6&lATO&r中使用,所以任何版本都适用？\\n\\n哦对了,是&a铀&r!\\n\\n开采&a&a铀矿石&f&r,并在一个&d&l&a富集仓&f&r中使用&a&a铀锭&f&r来制作&e&a铀黄饼&f&r.\\n\\n不,别吃它.它不是那种蛋糕!\\n\\n在&c&l化学氧化器&r中烘烤&e&a铀黄饼&f&r以制作&a&a氧化铀&f&r.\\n&7[Let's take a break from Sulfur and Acids and let's focus on the Radioactive part of Fissile Fuel! \\n\\nNow let's see... what is Radioactive, abundant, and used in lATO so any version will work? \\n\\nOh yeah Uranium! \\n\\nMine Uranium Ore and use the Uranium Ingots in an lEnrichment Chamber to make Yellow Cake Uranium. \\n\\nNo, don't eat it. It isn't that type of Cake! \\n\\nBake the Yellow Cake Uranium in a lChemical Oxidizier to make Uranium Oxide.]&f"]
	quest.302E9BC711779A4A.title: "制备&a铀&7[Preparing Uranium]&f"
	quest.32ABE5D734703B9C.quest_desc: ["&7鞘翅&r还是&a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r……\\n\\n&7鞘翅&r还是&a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r……\\n\\n为什么不全都要呢？\\n&7[Elytra or lMekaSuit Bodyarmor... \\n\\nElytra or lMekaSuit Bodyarmor... \\n\\nWhy not both?]&f"]
	quest.32ABE5D734703B9C.quest_subtitle: "身体护甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.32ABE5D734703B9C.title: "&7&a鞘翅单元&f&7[Elytra Unit]&f"
	quest.3526D444F81AD6D9.quest_desc: ["&dMeka工具&r已经比&6AllTheModium剑&r造成更多&a伤害&f了,但为什么不更多一点呢!\\n\\n我无法告诉你每个&7单元&r能增加多少,但肯定是你添加得越多,增加得就越多.\\n\\n就像锋利附魔一样!\\n&7[The Meka-Tool already does more Damage than an AllTheModium Sword, but why not a little more! \\n\\nI can't tell how much more each Unit gives, but it definitely increases the more you have added. \\n\\nJust like Sharpness!]&f"]
	quest.3526D444F81AD6D9.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.3526D444F81AD6D9.title: "&4攻击强化&7单元&7[Attack Amplification Unit]&f"
	quest.3561A33758A1E8C3.quest_desc: [
		"首先,我们建造.其次,我们启动.第三,我们使用.\\n\\n&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r的所有面都使用一个5格长的菱形结构.框架将由&c聚变&a反应堆外壳&f&r制成,内部可以由&a反应堆玻璃&f&r制成.\\n\\n&c&a聚变反应堆端口&f&r可以替换结构中的任何&a反应堆玻璃&f方块(除了需要其他方块的位置).\\n\\n&c&a激光聚焦矩阵&f&r也将放置在&a反应堆玻璃&f的位置.不过希望不要离其他方块太近!\\n\\n&c&a湮灭反应堆控制器&f&r,最重要的方块,将放置在最顶层的正方形中心.\\n\\n别担心,内部是空心的……我不建议在它运行时检查是否是空心的,那会杀了你.\\n&7[First, we build. Second, we start up. Third, we use. \\n\\nAll sides of the lFusion Reactor use a 5 Block long Diamond shape. The frame will be made of Fusion Reactor Casing and the inside can be made of Reactor Glass. \\n\\nThe Fusion Reactor Ports can replace any Reactor Glass Block in the Structure (besides where other Blocks are needed) \\n\\nThe Laser Focus Matrix will also be placed where Reactor Glass is. Hopefully not to close to other Blocks though! \\n\\nThe Fusion Reactor Controller, the most important Block, will be placed in the square center of the top layer. \\n\\nDon't worry the inside will be hollow... I don't recommend checking if it is when it's on, that'll kill you. ]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"砰!建好了!现在我们怎么让这个小家伙工作起来？\\n\\n首先,拿起你的&eHohlraum&r,它应该是装满的!然后把它放入&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r的GUI中.\\n\\n我们可以通过&a右击&f一个完全建好的反应堆的&c控制器&r来打开它的GUI.\\n\\n现在,除了装满的&eHohlraum&r,我们还需要扔进去一些燃料!\\n\\n然后,我们可以用至少1GFE的能量轰击&4&a激光增幅器&f&r,射入&c&a激光聚焦矩阵&f&r.\\n\\n现在它就可以使用了!\\n&7[BOOM! It is built! Now how do we get this puppy working? \\n\\nFirst, grab your Hohlraum, which should be filled! And place it within the GUI of the lFusion Reactor. \\n\\nWe can open its GUI by Right Clicking the Controller of a fully built one. \\n\\nNow along with the filled Hohlraum we'll need to throw some Fuel in! \\n\\nThen, we can blast the Laser Amplifier with atleast 1GFE, into the Laser Focus Matrix. \\n\\nNow it is ready for use! ]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"大部分使用都是通过&c控制器&r进行的.首先,我们进入主菜单.这只是用于&eHohlraum&r插槽,并告诉你它是否建造正确!\\n\\n接下来是热量菜单.这是关于&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r的&6温度&r有多高.这决定了产生多少&a能量&r或蒸汽!并且由射入其中的&4&a激光增幅器&f&r以及是否被冷却决定.\\n\\n我们可以用底部的按钮改变&6温度&r甚至&a能量&r的单位!\\n\\n下一个菜单是燃料菜单!它会显示&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r内有多少&c氘&r、&a氚&r和&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r.我们还可以改变注入速率,即每个游戏刻消耗多少燃料.\\n\\n统计菜单向我们展示了很多花哨的数字!它们只对书呆子重要,所以我们不会关注它们!\\n&7[Most of the use is through the Controller. First, we get the main menu. This is just for the Hohlraum slot, and telling you if it is built correctly! \\n\\nNext, is the Heat menu. This is for how Hot the Temperature of the lFusion Reactor is. This determines the amount of Energy or Steam is created! And is determined by the Laser Amplifier being shot into it, and if it is cooled. \\n\\nWe can change the Units of Temperature or even Energy with the bottom Buttons! \\n\\nNext menu, is for Fuel! It will show how much Deuterium, Tritium, and D-T Fuel is within the lFusion Reactor. We can also change the Inject Rate, how much Fuel is used up each Tick. \\n\\nStats menu shows us a lot of fancy numbers! They're only important to nerds so we won't focus on them!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fusion1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fusion2.png width:110 height:90 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fusion3.png width:110 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fusion4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fusion5.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.3561A33758A1E8C3.quest_subtitle: "将2种元素合为1种&7[Combining 2 Elements into 1]&f"
	quest.3561A33758A1E8C3.title: "&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&7[lFusion Reactor]&f"
	quest.35D9CD19EAADED6C.quest_desc: ["你知道&a辐射&r这东西可能非常致命!而且每个人都会犯错.\\n\\n但问题依然存在,你是愿意穿时髦但非常脆弱的&6&a防化服&f&r,还是……全能的&a&lMekaSuit&r配上&a&a辐射防护模块&f&7单元&r!\\n\\n如果所有&a&lMekaSuit部件&r都安装了&a&a辐射防护模块&f&7单元&r,你将能够在&a辐射&r中安全行走!\\n&7[You know that Radiation stuff can get pretty deadly! And everyone makes mistakes. \\n\\nBut the question remains, would you rather wear the stylish but very weak Hazmat Suit or... the all powerful lMekaSuit with Radiation Shielding Unit! \\n\\nIf all lMekaSuit Parts have the Radiation Shielding Unit installed, you'll be able to safely walk around in Radiation!]&f"]
	quest.35D9CD19EAADED6C.quest_subtitle: "所有护甲&7[All Armor]&f"
	quest.35D9CD19EAADED6C.title: "&a&a辐射防护模块&f &7Unit&7[Radiation Shielding Unit]&f"
	quest.369DADE3B3D8416F.quest_desc: ["不幸的是,&a氚&r不像&c氘&r那么容易获得……\\n\\n我们需要一个&6&l&a热力蒸馏塔&f&r.嗯……实际上需要2个.1个把&9水&r变成&e盐水&r,另一个把&e盐水&r变成&6锂&r.\\n\\n嗯……实际上是&6&a液态锂&f&r,我们需要&c化学&6锂&r.使用&c&l旋转冷凝器&r把它从&b液体&r变成&c化学&r形式!\\n\\n然后,我们可以使用&e&l&a太阳能中子活化器&f&r把&6锂&r变成&a氚&r.\\n\\n比&c氘&r难,但比&2&a裂变燃料&f&r容易.\\n&7[Tritium is unfortunately not as easy to get as Deuterium is... \\n\\nWe'll need a lThermal Evaporation Plant. Well... actually 2 of them. 1 to turn Water into Brine, the other to turn the Brine into Lithium. \\n\\nWell... actually Liquid Lithium, we need Chemical Lithium. Use the lRotary Condensator to turn it from Liquid to Chemical! \\n\\nThen, we can use the lSolar Neutron Activator to turn the Lithium into Tritium.\\n\\nHarder than Deuterium, but easier than Fissile Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.369DADE3B3D8416F.quest_subtitle: "T&7[T]&f"
	quest.369DADE3B3D8416F.title: "&a氚&7[Tritium]&f"
	quest.3B936CA3F0F7B26B.quest_desc: ["&l&7&a数字型采矿机&f&r是一个3x2x3的……方块？&5机器&r？\\n\\n我们都知道&a虚空矿工&f,但得了吧,那些东西很奇怪!这个开采的是真正的方块!\\n\\n我们可以&a右击&f它来打开它的GUI,在这里我们可以看到一大堆东西!按钮、屏幕,甚至还有插槽!\\n\\n插槽是开采的&e物品&r将去往的地方.&a屏幕&f会告诉你它是否就绪、&a能量&r不足,或者它能开采多少个方块.屏幕内还有按钮可以自动弹出、吸走它开采的方块,甚至使用&a精准采集&f!\\n\\n&a按钮&f会处理其他所有事情!我们可以使用可视化功能来查看将被开采的区域.或者甚至添加升级来让它变得更好!\\n\\n开始:会告诉&l&7&a数字型采矿机&f&r开始采矿!如果&5机器&r没有就绪,它将不会工作.停止:会告诉&l&7&a数字型采矿机&f&r停止采矿.配置:设置过滤器,这很重要.重置:&a已损坏&f.\\n\\n配置的左侧设置采矿的工作区域.多远、多高、多低!右侧是实际的&e物品&r过滤器.&a过滤器&f与&e&lQIO&r&e导入器&f和&e导出器&r相同,查看它们的任务来学习如何设置那些!\\n\\n你也可以使用反转模式来将过滤器设为黑名单.还有替换功能,可以填充被开采的方块.\\n&7[The lDigital Miner is a 3x2x3... Block? Machine? \\n\\nWe all know of Void Miners but come on those are weird! This Mines actual Blocks! \\n\\nWe can Right Click it to open it's GUI, here we can see a whole bunch! Buttons, Screens, and even Slots! \\n\\nSlots are where the Mined Items will go to. The Screen will tell if it is ready, doesn't have enough Energy, or how many Blocks it can Mine. It also has Buttons within the Screen to Auto-Eject, suck up the Blocks it Mines, and even use Silk Touch! \\n\\nThe Buttons will do everything else! We can use Visuals to see the area that will be Mined. Or even add Upgrades to make it better! \\n\\nStart: will tell the lDigital Miner to start Mining! It won't work if the Machine isn't ready. Stop: will tell the lDigital Miner to stop Mining. Config: sets Filters, this is important. Reset: is broken. \\n\\nConfigs left side sets the Working Area for the Mining. How far, high, and low! The right side is for the actual Item Filter. The Filter is the same as with lQIO Importers and Exporters, check out their Quest to learn how to set those! \\n\\nYou can also use Inverse Mode to Blacklist the Filters. Plus Replacements which will fill in the Mined Blocks. ]&f"]
	quest.3B936CA3F0F7B26B.title: "&l&7&a数字型采矿机&f&7[lDigital Miner]&f"
	quest.3CCBE9BBCA8ADA38.quest_desc: ["&d&l超临界&a相移&fe&r需要大量&a能量&r.我是说非常多!数亿FE.\\n\\n不过我们如何输送这么多&a能量&r呢？\\n\\n我们至少需要1个(推荐2个)&d超导线圈&r!\\n\\n&d超导线圈&r被放置在&d&lS.P.S.&r内部,在一个&d&a超临界移相器端口&f&r上.&d端口&r需要为&d超导线圈&r提供&a能量&r.\\n\\n每个&d超导线圈&r每游戏刻可以输入400MFE.而我们需要一大堆这样的东西来生产&d反物质&r!\\n&7[The lSuper-Critical Phase Shifter will need a lot of Energy. I mean a lot a lot! Hundreds of Millions of FE. \\n\\nHow do we deliver this much Energy though? \\n\\nWe'll need atleast 1 (recommended 2) Supercharged Coils! \\n\\nThe Supercharged Coil is placed inside the lS.P.S., on an SPS Port. The Port will need to feed the Supercharged Coil Energy. \\n\\nEach Supercharged Coil can send in 400MFE per Tick. And we'll need a whole lotta those for Antimatter!]&f"]
	quest.3CCBE9BBCA8ADA38.title: "&d超导线圈&7[Supercharged Coils]&f"
	quest.3D2B4D9FD2086B9B.quest_desc: ["&2&a裂变反应堆逻辑适配器&f&r,我将称之为&2FRLA&r,用于通过&4红石&r监控和配置&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r.\\n\\n首先,像放置&2端口&r一样,将&2FRLA&r放置在&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r的一面墙上.\\n\\n然后,我们可以&a右击&f&2FRLA&r来配置它.\\n\\n禁用:不会与&4红石&r交互.\\n\\n激活:当收到&4&a红石信号&f&r时会打开&2&l反应堆&f&r,当&4信号&f&r消失时会关闭.\\n\\n&a高温&f:当&6温度&f&r达到危险水平时会发出&4&a红石信号&f&r.\\n\\n临界废料水平:当&8&a核废料&f&r过多时会发出&4信号&f&r.\\n\\n&a损伤临界值&f:和其他一样,当&2&l反应堆&f&r即将爆炸时会发出&4信号&f&r!\\n\\n燃料不足:当&2&a裂变燃料&f&r即将耗尽时会发出&4信号&f&r.\\n&7[The Fission Reactor Logic Adapter ,which I will be calling FRLA, is used to monitor and configure the lFission Reactor with Redstone. \\n\\nFirst, place the FRLA in one of the walls of the lFission Reactor like you would with the Ports. \\n\\nThen, we can Right Click the FRLA to configure it. \\n\\nDisabled: won't interact with Redstone. \\n\\nActivation: will turn the lReactor on when given a Redstone Signal, and when there is no longer a Signal it will turn off. \\n\\nHigh Temperature: will send out a Redstone Signal when the Temperatures reach a dangerous Level. \\n\\nCritical Waste Level: will give a Signal when there is too much Nuclear Waste. \\n\\nDamage Critical: will, like the others, will give out a Signal when the lReactor is just about to blow up! \\n\\nInsufficient Fuel: will give a Signal when it is running out of Fissile Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.3D2B4D9FD2086B9B.title: "&2&a裂变反应堆逻辑适配器&f&7[Fission Reactor Logic Adapter]&f"
	quest.3E5BE6D6422F682C.quest_desc: ["我们的&9&l涡轮机&r需要输入蒸汽,输出&9水&r和&a能量&r.\\n\\n但是怎么做呢？\\n\\n我们可以使用&9涡轮机端口&r来引入蒸汽并输出&a能量&r.不过我们需要使用&9&a涡轮排气口&f&r来输出&9水&r!\\n\\n这两者都放置在我们的&9&l涡轮机&r的墙壁内.\\n&7[Our lTurbine will need Steam in, Water out, and Energy out. \\n\\nBut how? \\n\\nWe can use Turbine Ports to bring in Steam and take out Energy. We'll need to use the Turbine Vents to take out Water though! \\n\\nBoth of these are placed within the Walls of our lTurbines.]&f"]
	quest.3E5BE6D6422F682C.title: "&9&l涡轮机&r输入与输出&7[lTurbine Inputs and Outputs]&f"
	quest.40B24676E11D9410.quest_desc: ["我们需要大量矿石用于&5&l&d通用机械&f&r,所以为什么不升级我们的&dMeka工具&r来获得更多呢!\\n\\n&d&a矿石提炼&f&r将像时运附魔一样工作.当矿石被开采时,有几率获得更多&a掉落物&f.\\n\\n不过我们不能将&b&a精准采集&f&7单元&r与这个一起使用.要么是矿石方块,要么是矿石掉落物,选一个!\\n&7[We need lots of Ores for lMekanism so why not upgrade our Meka-Tool to get more! \\n\\nOre Refinement will act like Fortune. When Ores are Mined, there is a chance to get more Drops from them. \\n\\nWe can't use the Silk Touch Unit with this one though. Either Ore Blocks or Ore Drops, choose 1!]&f"]
	quest.40B24676E11D9410.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.40B24676E11D9410.title: "&d&a矿石提炼&f&7单元&7[Ore Refinement Unit]&f"
	quest.40E8940C92668D4F.quest_desc: ["&c氘&r实际上相对容易获得!\\n\\n首先,我们需要&9&a重水&f&r.&9&a重水&f&r就像普通的水H2O,只是H有点不同!\\n\\n我们可以在&9&l电动泵&r(显然要在&9水&r上方)中使用&9过滤器&8升级&r来提取&9&a重水&f&r而不是&9水&r.\\n\\n在&9&l&a电解分离器&f&r中&a处理&f&9&a重水&f&r会给我们&b氧气&r和&c氘&r,而不是&7氢气&r.\\n\\n告诉过你这很简单!\\n&7[Deuterium is actually relatively simple to get! \\n\\nFirst, we need Heavy Water. Heavy Water is just like good ol' H2O, just the H is a little different! \\n\\nWe can use the Filter Upgrade in an lElectric Pump (obviously above Water) to extract Heavy Water instead of Water. \\n\\nProcessing the Heavy Water through an lElectrolytic Separator will give us Oxygen and Deuterium instead of Hydrogen. \\n\\nTold ya it's simple!]&f"]
	quest.40E8940C92668D4F.quest_subtitle: "D&7[D]&f"
	quest.40E8940C92668D4F.title: "&c氘&7[Deuterium]&f"
	quest.4211F29561F21643.quest_desc: ["&9&l涡轮机&r的工作方式是它通过&9端口&r吸入蒸汽,这些蒸汽会推动&9转子&r上的&9叶片&r.\\n\\n哦等等,我可能应该告诉你如何创建&9&l涡轮机&r的内部结构!\\n\\n&9转子&r将从地板向上放置在我们&9&l涡轮机&r的正中心.每个&9转子&r可以容纳2个&9叶片&r.\\n\\n&9叶片&r和&9转子&r越多,它就会变得越宽.我们将无法在更大的内部结构中使用5x5的底座.\\n\\n在我们最高的&9转子&r顶部,我们将放置&9&a复杂旋钮装置&f&r.相信我,这很重要!\\n&7[The way the lTurbine works is it takes in Steam via the Ports and that Steam will move the Blades on the Rotors. \\n\\nOh wait I should probably tell you how to create the lTurbine insides! \\n\\nThe Rotors will be placed from the floor up within the exact center of our lTurbines. Each Rotor can hold 2 Blades. \\n\\nThe more Blades and Rotors the wider it will get. We won't be able to use 5x5 Base with bigger insides. \\n\\nOn top of our highest Rotor we'll place the Rotational Complex. Trust me it is important!]&f"]
	quest.4211F29561F21643.title: "运动部件&7[Moving parts]&f"
	quest.438F734D16DA9638.quest_desc: ["我们有了&a钋&r,剩下的应该是我们已经有的东西!\\n\\n一个&2&lP.R.C.&r、&9水&r和&d&a氟石粉&f&r!\\n\\n将1,000mB&9水&r与1,000mB&a钋&r和1个&d&a氟石粉&f&r结合,制作1个&a&a钋靶丸&f&r和1,000mB&8废&a核废料&f&r.\\n\\n&d&a氟石粉&f&r可以像任何&a金属粉末&f一样制作:&4&l粉碎机&r、&d&l&a富集仓&f&r,甚至矿石锤!\\n&7[We got our Polonium and the rest is what we should already have! \\n\\nA lP.R.C., Water, and Fluorite Dust! \\n\\nCombine 1,000mB Water, with 1,000mB Polonium, and 1 Fluorite Dust to make 1 Polonium Pellet and 1,000mB Spent Nuclear Waste. \\n\\nFluorite Dust can be made like any Metal Dust: lCrusher, lEnrichment Chamber, or even an Ore Hammer!]&f"]
	quest.438F734D16DA9638.title: "&a&a钋靶丸&f&7[Polonium Pellets]&f"
	quest.43DB0CFC5F5B0967.quest_desc: ["&a剂量计&r将显示你体内当前有多少SVP单位的&a辐射&r.\\n是的,在你体内.\\n\\n记住你可以启用和禁用它来清理HUD上的空间!\\n&7[The Dosimeter will show how many SVP Units of Radiation are currently in you. \\nYes, in you. \\n\\nRemember you can enable and disable it to clear up room in your HUD!]&f"]
	quest.43DB0CFC5F5B0967.quest_subtitle: "身体护甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.43DB0CFC5F5B0967.title: "&a剂量计&7单元&7[Dosimeter Unit]&f"
	quest.4447EEEB8D762721.quest_desc: ["&4激光消散&7单元&r将升级&a&lMekaSuit&r.嗯,是它的每个部件.\\n\\n当你走进&4激光&r时,它们不会造成任何&a伤害&f,而不是快速杀死你!\\n\\n实际上会有一小部分&4激光&r直接穿过你!不是全部.\\n&7[The Laser Dissipation Units will upgrade the lMekaSuit. Well each piece of it. \\n\\nInstead of quickly killing you when you walk into Lasers, they won't cause any Damage at all! \\n\\nA little bit of the Laser will actually pass right through you! Not all of it.]&f"]
	quest.4447EEEB8D762721.quest_subtitle: "所有护甲&7[All Armor]&f"
	quest.4447EEEB8D762721.title: "&4激光消散&7单元&7[Laser Dissipation Unit]&f"
	quest.459AEC4C2A611824.quest_desc: ["致所有不使用&a&a夜视&f&r &a资源包&f作弊的玩家,这个可能对你们有帮助!\\n\\n这个&7模块单元&r会在你佩戴&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r时给你一些&a&a夜视&f&r效果.\\n\\n虽然确实,很多&e物品&r让这个功能显得无用,但我还是要告诉你!\\n&7[To all Players who don't cheat by using Night Vision Resource Packs, this might be helpful! \\n\\nThis Module Unit will give you some Night Vision when you wear the lMekaSuit Helmet. \\n\\nWhile yes, lots of Items make this useless, I'm still going to tell you about it!]&f"]
	quest.459AEC4C2A611824.quest_subtitle: "头盔&7[Helmet]&f"
	quest.459AEC4C2A611824.title: "&a&a视觉增强&f&7单元&7[Vision Enhancement Unit]&f"
	quest.4869D9DBDD1A15CD.quest_desc: ["&cC&6o&el&ao&br &cM&6o&ed&au&bl&ca&6t&ei&ao&bn &7单元&r将允许你改变其所在的&a&lMekaSuit部件&r的&cC&6o&el&ao&b&r.\\n\\n只需手持&e物品&r并按(\\\\)即可访问其配置.\\n\\n我们有多少种&cC&6o&el&ao&b&r可用？我不知道,我们有多少种带十六进制代码的&cC&6o&el&ao&b&r!\\n\\n不过,这只影响那个&a&lMekaSuit部件&r,每个&a&lMekaSuit部件&r都需要自己的&7单元&r.\\n&7[The Color Modulation Unit will allow you to change the Color of the lMekaSuit Part it is in. \\n\\nJust hold the Item and press (\\\\\\) in order to access its Configs. \\n\\nHow many Colors do we have available? I don't know, how many Colors do we have with the Hex Codes! \\n\\nThis will only effect that lMekaSuit Part though, each lMekaSuit Part will need their own Units.]&f"]
	quest.4869D9DBDD1A15CD.quest_subtitle: "所有盔甲&7[All Armor]&f"
	quest.4869D9DBDD1A15CD.title: "&cC&6o&el&ao&br &cM&6o&ed&au&bl&ca&6t&ei&ao&bn &7单元&7[Color Modulation Unit]&f"
	quest.48F496BD0FFE5A34.quest_desc: ["&4磁性 &9吸引 &7单元&r的工作原理就像简单的磁铁.当使用/穿戴时,它会将超出范围的&e物品&r吸引向你.\\n\\n&4磁性 &9吸引 &7单元&r越多,能被拉向你的&e物品&r距离就越远.\\n&7[The Magnetic Attraction Unit works just like a Simple Magnet. When used/worn, it will attract Items toward you that are out of range. \\n\\nThe more Magnetic Attraction Units the farther Items can be that will be pulled toward you.]&f"]
	quest.48F496BD0FFE5A34.quest_subtitle: "靴子&7[Boots]&f"
	quest.48F496BD0FFE5A34.title: "&4磁性 &9吸引 &7单元&7[Magnetic Attraction Unit]&f"
	quest.4926C95DD02F1410.quest_desc: ["你见过那些用信标当&4激光安全门&r的教程吧？然后当你自己尝试时,却发现它根本杀不了人,是不是很失望？\\n\\n而&4激光&r就能做到!\\n\\n相信我,它们看起来像信标,但绝对致命!\\n\\n不过和信标不同,你不能用玻璃改变它的颜色.很可能是因为它们会摧毁几乎所有挡路的方块,并且掉落物也会消失……\\n\\n它们还需要消耗&a能量&r,而不是材料来供能.\\n\\n我不知道它们具体造成多少&a伤害&f,但足以让一只鸡在碰到&4激光&r的瞬间就被烤熟!\\n&7[You ever see those Tutorials that use Beacons as a Laser Security Gate. Then, when you try it you get disappointed it doesn't kill people? \\n\\nWell Lasers do just that! \\n\\nTrust me, they look like Beacons and they definitely kill! \\n\\nUnlike Beacons though, you can't change its Color with Glass. Most likely because they break almost every Block that gets in their way and Voids the drops... \\n\\nThey also use Energy instead of Materials to get powered. \\n\\nI don't know the exact amount of Damage they do but they do enough to Fry a Chicken the instant it touches the Laser!]&f"]
	quest.4926C95DD02F1410.title: "&4激光&7[Lasers]&f"
	quest.4B2835706B593E9A.quest_desc: ["&d&l反质子&5核合成器&r是一台由&d&a反物质靶丸&f&r制成的&5机器&r.\\n\\n当然,它也用&d反物质&r作为燃料,因为成本还不够高!\\n\\n那么它能做什么呢？\\n\\n利用我们的&d反物质&r、&a能量&r和某个特定的&e物品&r,来创造一种全新的(通常很稀有的)&e物品&r.有些甚至无法合成!\\n\\n比如把&5紫水晶&f变成&9&a回响碎片&f&f,把&e&a金苹果&f&f变成&e&a附魔金苹果&f&r,甚至把鸡蛋变成&d&a龙蛋&f&r!\\n&7[lAntiprotonic Nucleosynthesizer is a Machine made from Antimatter Pellets. \\n\\nOf course it also uses Antimatter as Fuel as well, because it wasn't expensive enough! \\n\\nSo what does it do? \\n\\nWith our Antimatter, Energy, and a certain Item to create a brand new (and usually rare) Item. Some we can't even Craft! \\n\\nLike Amethyst to Echo Shards, Golden Apple to Enchanted Golden Apple, and even Eggs to the Dragon Egg!]&f"]
	quest.4B2835706B593E9A.title: "&d&l反质子&5核合成器&7[lAntiprotonic Nucleosynethesizer]&f"
	quest.4BAF44FCA0894DE8.quest_desc: ["和&5&l&a同位素离心机&f&r一样,&e&l&a太阳能中子活化器&f&r只用于两种配方,其中一种还涉及&8&a核废料&f&r!\\n\\n这台&5机器&r会通过顶部的&e&a太阳能电池板&f&r吸收&e太阳&r光线.然后将这些光线聚焦成一束,照射在&8&a核废料&f&r上.\\n\\n这也意味着它在&9夜晚&r无法工作……\\n\\n每5mB的&8&a核废料&f&r会变成1mB的&a钋&r.\\n\\n所以你需要5,000mB的&2&a裂变燃料&f&r来制造5,000mB的&8&a核废料&f&r.\\n&7[Like the lIsotopic Centrifuge, the lSolar Neutron Activator is only used for 2 Recipes and 1 of them is with Nuclear Waste! \\n\\nThis Machine will take in the Sun's Rays through the Solar Cells on top. It will then focus those Rays into one Beam and use it on the Nuclear Waste. \\n\\nThis also makes it so it doesn't work at Nighttime... \\n\\nEvery 5mB of Nuclear Waste will become 1mB of Polonium. \\n\\nSo you'll need 5,000mB of Fissile Fuel to make 5,000mB of Nuclear Waste.]&f"]
	quest.4BAF44FCA0894DE8.title: "利用&e太阳&r制造&a钋&7[Using the Sun to make Polonium]&f"
	quest.4E18E28BDF6B7983.quest_desc: ["&c&a聚变反应堆端口&f&r将替换&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r内部的&a反应堆玻璃&f,以便使用.\\n\\n我们需要几个&c端口&r.2个(或1个)用于输入燃料&c氘&r和&a氚&r(或者直接用&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r).还需要1个用于输出&a能量&r.\\n\\n如果你想用&9水&r冷却&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r,就需要另外2个&c端口&r.1个用于输入&9水&r,1个用于输出蒸汽.\\n\\n和其他端口一样,我们可以用&3配置器&r来设置&c端口&r是输入还是输出!\\n&7[Fusion Reactor Ports will replace the Reactor Glass within the lFusion Reactor in order to be used. \\n\\nWe'll need a few Ports. 2 (or 1) for Deuterium and Tritium (or just D-T Fuel) for Fuel. We'll also need 1 for Outputting Energy. \\n\\nIf you want to use Water to cool the lFusion Reactor, you'll need 2 more Ports. 1 for Inputting Water and 1 for Outputting Steam. \\n\\nLike other Ports, we can use the Configurator to set whether the Port Inputs or Outputs!]&f"]
	quest.4E18E28BDF6B7983.title: "&c&a聚变反应堆端口&f&7[Fusion Reactor Ports]&f"
	quest.4F9C8D90ACF563F5.quest_desc: ["感谢&2&lMinecraft&r的海洋更新,但游泳有时还是很慢.\\n\\n所以为什么不加速呢!就像&a深海探索者&f一样!\\n\\n有了&9流体静压斥力&7单元&r,你可以在&9水中走得更快,游得更快.\\n&7[Thank you lMinecraft for the Update Aquatic, but Swimming can still be very slow. \\n\\nSo why not speed it up! Just like Depth Strider! \\n\\nWith the Hydrostatic Repulsor Unit you can Walk and Swim faster in Water.]&f"]
	quest.4F9C8D90ACF563F5.quest_subtitle: "护腿&7[Pants]&f"
	quest.4F9C8D90ACF563F5.title: "&9流体静压斥力&7单元&7[Hydrostatic Repulsor Unit]&f"
	quest.50F23B2688D7E699.quest_desc: ["将1,000mB的&d反物质&r通过&5&l&a化学结晶器&f&r处理,我们可以制造1个&d&a反物质靶丸&f&r.\\n\\n这意味着需要1,000,000mB的&a钋&r,或者说1MmB的&a钋&r.\\n\\n要获得所有这些&a钋&r,你需要5,000,000mB的&8&a核废料&f&r,以及制造这些&8&a核废料&f&r所需的&2&a裂变燃料&f&r.仅仅5MmB的&2&a裂变燃料&f&r……而已!\\n\\n但最终,我们得到了!这是整个&5&l&d通用机械&f&r中最珍贵的&e物品&r!&d&a反物质靶丸&f&r.\\n\\n我们现在可以制造MekaSuit套装,为&e&lQIO&r增加更多存储空间,甚至制造&6&l&aATM之星&f&r!\\n&7[With 1,000mB of Antimatter processed through a lChemical Crystallizer we can make 1 Antimatter Pellet. \\n\\nThat means it takes 1,000,000mB Polonium or 1MmB Polonium. \\n\\nFor all that Polonium you'll need 5,000,000mB Nuclear Waste and Fissile Fuel to make the Nuclear Waste. Only 5MmB Fissile Fuel... only! \\n\\nBut finally, we have it! The most valued Item in all of lMekanism! The Antimatter Pellet. \\n\\nWe can now make our MekaSuit, more storage for the lQIO, and even the lATM Star!]&f"]
	quest.5194A067BEA98E79.quest_desc: ["嘿,我记得你!\\n\\n事实证明,&5&l&a同位素离心机&f&r用于两种配方.&2&a裂变燃料&f&r和&3钚&r!\\n\\n&a循环检测&f 5mB的&8&a核废料&f&r,我们可以制造1mB的&3钚&r.\\n\\n如果每个&3&a钚靶丸&f&r相当于1,000mB的&3钚&r,那么我们需要5,000mB的&8&a核废料&f&r,以及等量的&2&a裂变燃料&f&r.\\n&7[Hey, I remember you! \\n\\nTurns out, the lIsotopic Centrifuge is used for 2 Recipes. Fissile Fuel and Plutonium! \\n\\nFor each 5mB of Nuclear Waste we can create 1mB of Plutonium. \\n\\nIf each Plutonium Pellets are 1,000mB worth of Plutonium, then we'll need 5,000mB of Nuclear Waste and the same for Fissile Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.5194A067BEA98E79.title: "离心分离&3钚&7[Spinning for Plutonium]&f"
	quest.52B3955A80DB0B4A.quest_desc: ["&6爆破&r和&2&l原版&r附魔不沾边,但更接近模组内容!\\n\\n一旦安装,我们可以调整它的配置,改变我们能够挖掘的方块区域大小.\\n\\n默认是1x1,也就是1个方块.我们可以改成3x3、5x5、7x7和9x9.\\n\\n是的,挖掘一个9x9的区域会比挖掘单个方块消耗更多&a能量&r.\\n&7[Blasting isn't close to lVanilla Enchantments, but closer to Modded! \\n\\nOnce Installed, we can mess with its Configs to change how big of a square of Blocks we can Mine. \\n\\nDefault is 1x1 aka 1 Block. We can change it to 3x3, 5x5, 7x7, and 9x9. \\n\\nYes, Mining a 9x9 square will take more Energy than Mining a single Block.]&f"]
	quest.52B3955A80DB0B4A.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.52B3955A80DB0B4A.title: "&6爆破&7单元&7[Blasting Unit]&f"
	quest.53E929BF89209CFC.quest_desc: ["&e输入总线&f和&e输出总线&r可以用来自动向&e&lQIO系统&r导入和导出&e物品&r.\\n\\n&e输入总线&f和&e输出总线&r都需要放置在带有物品栏的方块上,以便取出或放入&e物品&r.它们还需要设置为与&e&l&aQIO驱动器阵列&f&r相同的网络.\\n\\n如果它们被设置为导入或导出但没有过滤器,它们会自动从相应的物品栏或系统中取出(或放入)所有&e物品&r.\\n\\n如果你想过滤,可以使用物品堆、标签和模组.每种方式都需要将一个&e物品&r放入对应的槽位来设置.物品堆将只使用该&e物品&r.标签需要在文本框中输入物品标签.模组将使用&e物品&r所属的模组.比如&2&lMinecraft&r代表所有&2&l原版&r方块.\\n&7[Importers and Exporters can be used to automatically Import and Export Items from and to the lQIO System. \\n\\nImporters and Exporters are both Placed on Blocks with Inventories in order to take or give Items. They'll also need to be set to the same Network as the lQIO Drive Array. \\n\\nIf they are set to Import or Export without Filters, they will automatically take in (or out) every Item in the respected Inventories or System. \\n\\nIf you want to Filter, you use Itemstack, Tag, and Mod. Each are set by putting an Item into the Slot. Itemstack will use only that Item. Tag will need the Item Tag typed into the Text Box. Mod will use the Mod an Item is from. Like lMinecraft for all lVanilla Blocks.]&f"]
	quest.53E929BF89209CFC.title: "导入与导出&7[Import and Export]&f"
	quest.54E0B946BAC13654.quest_desc: [
		"从技术上讲,我们能制造的最小(可工作的)&a&l充能&a输导矩阵&f&r只需要1个&a感应仓&f和&a感应供应器&r,但所有矩阵的制造方式都一样.\\n\\n我们需要用&a&a输导外壳&f&r搭建一个至少3x4x3到18x18x18的框架.\\n\\n墙壁、天花板和地板可以用&a&a输导外壳&f&r、结构玻璃/&a反应堆玻璃&f或&a&a输导端口&f&r填充.\\n\\n&a&l&a输导矩阵&f&r的内部将由我们的&a感应仓&f和&a供应器&r构成.\\n\\n如果我们使用18x18x18的尺寸,我们将有4,096个空间来放置&a感应仓&f和&a供应器&r.所以如果我们把空间平均分配给两者,我们可以得到……3.28QFE的存储容量和每游戏刻107GFE的输入/输出速率.\\n&7[Technically the smallest (working) lEnergized Induction Matrix we can make only has 1 Induction Cell and Induction Provider but all are made the same way. \\n\\nWe'll need to make a frame of Induction Casings atleast 3x4x3 to 18x18x18. \\n\\nThe Walls, Ceiling, and Floor can be filled with Induction Casing, Structural/Reactor Glass, or Induction Ports. \\n\\nThe inside of the lInduction Matrix will be made of our Induction Cells and Providers. \\n\\nIf we use the 18x18x18 size, we'll have 4,096 Space to place Cells and Providers. So if we split it in half between the two we can get... a Storage of 3.28QFE and an Input/Output of 107GFE per Tick.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这个多方块结构可以做成任何可用尺寸,不仅仅是图片中展示的那样.&a相片&f仅仅展示了我们能制造的最小尺寸.\\n&7[This Multiblock can be made at any size available, not just what is shown through the Images. The Images merely show the smallest size we can make.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_matrix1.png width:100 height:75 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_matrix2.png width:100 height:90 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_matrix3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_matrix4.png width:100 height:110 align:center}"
	]
	quest.54E0B946BAC13654.title: "&a&l充能&a输导矩阵&f&7[lEnergized Induction Matrix]&f"
	quest.55702BE0151D33FE.quest_desc: ["&a&a输导端口&f&r是我们将&a能量&r输入和输出&a&l充能&a输导矩阵&f&r的方式.\\n\\n就像几乎所有多方块结构一样,你需要将&a端口&r放置在&a&l&a输导矩阵&f&r的墙壁内.\\n\\n我认为&a端口&r除了受&a&l&a输导矩阵&f&r本身的限制外没有其他限制,所以你不需要超过2个,除非你要从不同来源输入/输出!\\n&7[Induction Ports are how we'll get our Energy in and out of our lEnergized Induction Matrix. \\n\\nLike in what seems to be every single Multiblock, you'll need to place the Ports within the Walls of the lInduction Matrix. \\n\\nI don't believe the Ports have limits besides what the lInduction Matrix has, so you won't need more than 2 unless you're taking from different sources!]&f"]
	quest.55702BE0151D33FE.title: "&a&a输导端口&f&7[Induction Ports]&f"
	quest.56DB53F255100136.quest_desc: ["你需要更花哨的护腿？不如把我们的&5难以获取护腿&r升级成&a&l&aMekaSuit裤子&f&r吧!\\n\\n这也会消耗一个&d&a反物质靶丸&f&r、一个&d&a终极输导元件&f&r和一些&a&a钋靶丸&f&r.\\n\\n这个升级值得吗？它的护甲值居然和&c&a下界合金护腿&f&r一样？!？而且这应该是&c下界合金&r之后的第4次升级了!\\n\\n是的……它……值得!我们可以给&a&l&aMekaSuit裤子&f&r充电,当你受到&a伤害&f时,&a&l&aMekaSuit裤子&f&r会消耗&a能量&r来抵挡伤害!嗯,除了&a魔法伤害&f以外的所有伤害……\\n\\n然后,在&7&l&a改造站&f&r中使用它来添加&7模块单元&r,这些模块主要提升你的移动能力.是的,这真的非常重要!\\n&7[You need even fancier Pants? How about we upgrade our 难得素 leggings into lMekaSuit Pants! \\n\\nThis will also cost an Antimatter Pellet, an Ultimate Induction Cells, and a few Polonium Pellets. \\n\\nIs the upgrade worth it? It only has the same Armor stats as Netherite Leggings?!? And these should be 4 upgrades after Netherite! \\n\\nYes... it... is! We can Charge the lMekaSuit Pants and instead of you taking Damage, the lMekaSuit Pants will use up Energy! Well all Damage except Magic Damage... \\n\\nThen, use it in a lModification Station to add Module Units which mostly upgrade your Movement. Yeah, that can be pretty darn important!]&f"]
	quest.56DB53F255100136.title: "&a&l&aMekaSuit裤子&f&7[lMekaSuit Pants]&f"
	quest.58B5EF8EB72934C2.quest_desc: ["&c喷气背包&7单元&r会让你表现得像穿着&5&l&d通用机械&f&r的&c喷气背包&r和你的&a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r一样.\\n\\n&c喷气背包&r使用相同的控制方式,并且需要&7氢气&r作为燃料.\\n\\n你可以通过两种方式给它加注&7氢气&r.你可以把它放在装有&7氢气&r的&5机器&r里.或者当你的&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r装有&9&l电解呼吸&r模块时,待在&9水&r下.\\n\\n当你装有&d重力调节&7单元&r时,你将无法使用这个&7单元&r.\\n&7[The Jetpack Unit will act as if you are wearing the lMekanism Jetpack and your lMekaSuit Bodyarmor. \\n\\nThe Jetpack uses the same Controls, and will need Hydrogen as fuel. \\n\\nYou can fuel it with Hydrogen in 2 ways. You can place it in a Machine that has Hydrogen in it. Or be under Water while your lMekaSuit Helmet has lElectrolytic Breathing. \\n\\nYou won't be able to use this Unit while you have the Gravitational Modulating Unit on.]&f"]
	quest.58B5EF8EB72934C2.quest_subtitle: "胸甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.58B5EF8EB72934C2.title: "&c喷气背包&7单元&7[Jetpack Unit]&f"
	quest.593CB120B657126C.quest_desc: ["现在我们终于要担心&a放射性&r了!\\n\\n&8&a核废料&f&r(及其产物)具有&a放射性&r.这意味着它们必须存放在&e&a放射性废料桶&f&r中.\\n\\n&8&a核废料&f&r(及其产物)必须通过管道输入和输出&e&a放射性废料桶&f&r.\\n\\n你不能破坏装有&a放射性&r材料的&e桶&r或&c管道&r,否则&a辐射&r会在世界中扩散.\\n\\n&a放射性&r也可能来自&2&l反应堆&r泄漏或熔毁.\\n\\n我们如何应对&a放射性&r？&6&a防化服&f&r和时间.查看它自己的任务来了解更多信息!\\n&7[Now we can finally worry about Radioactivity! \\n\\nNuclear Waste (and it's products) are Radioactive. That means they must be held within Radioactive Waste Barrels. \\n\\nThe Nuclear Waste (and it's products) must be Tubed into and out of the Radioactive Waste Barrels. \\n\\nYou can not break the Barrel or Tubes that hold Radioactive materials, or else the Radiation will spread in the World. \\n\\nRadioactivity can also come from lReactors leaking or melting down. \\n\\nHow do we deal with Radioactivity? Hazmat Suit and time. Check out its own Quest to learn more about them!]&f"]
	quest.593CB120B657126C.title: "&a放射性&7[Radioactivity]&f"
	quest.5A088F8402230BA5.quest_desc: ["&2&a裂变反应堆端口&f&r非常重要.&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r需要用于&2燃料&f、&b冷却剂&f和&8废料&r的端口……所以没有&2端口&r它就无法工作.\\n\\n&2端口&r可以放置在&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r墙壁的任何部分,但不能放在边缘.\\n\\n我们需要4个端口,并且需要使用&3配置器&r对&2端口&r进行配置.\\n\\n它们初始状态为&a仅输入&r,但用&3配置器&r按住Shift键&a右击&f&2端口&r,会切换到&e输出废料&r,然后再切换到&b输出冷却剂&r.\\n\\n&a仅输入&r会同时输入&2&a裂变燃料&f&r和&b冷却剂&r,冷却剂可以是&9水&r或钠.\\n\\n&e输出废料&r会将&8&a核废料&f&r从&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r中排出.\\n\\n&b输出冷却剂&r会排出蒸汽(如果使用&9水&r作为&b冷却剂&r),或者如果使用钠,则会排出&6&a过热钠&f&r.\\n&7[Fission Reactor Ports are pretty darn important. The lFission Reactor will need Ports for Fuel, Coolant, and Waste... so it won't work without Ports. \\n\\nPorts can be placed within any parts of the lFission Reactor's Walls, just not on the edge. \\n\\nWe'll need to have 4 of them and we'll need to use the Configurator on the Ports to Configure them. \\n\\nThey will start as Input Only but by Shift Right Clicking the Ports with the Configurator it will switch to Output Waste and then to Output Coolant. \\n\\nInput Only will take in both Fissile Fuel and Coolant as either Water or Sodium. \\n\\nOutput Waste will send Nuclear Waste out of the lFission Reactor. \\n\\nOutput Coolant will either take out Steam if Water was used as the Coolant or if Sodium is used it will take out Superheated Sodium.]&f"]
	quest.5A088F8402230BA5.title: "&2&a裂变反应堆端口&f&7[Fission Reactor Port]&f"
	quest.5A4C9F7F81D6B9DB.quest_desc: ["&5重力调节附加&7单元&r,顾名思义,是&d重力调节&7单元&r的升级版.\\n\\n两者都需要安装才能使用!\\n\\n那么这些升级是什么呢？嗯,你在飞行中松开移动键时会立即停止.你可以更快地上升!甚至可以一直飞行!\\n&7[Gravitational Modulating Additional Unit, as you can tell by the name is an upgrade to the Gravitational Modulating Unit. \\n\\nBoth will need to be Installed to use them! \\n\\nSo what are these Upgrades? Well you will instantly stop when you stop holding your Movement Keys in Flight. You can ascend faster! And even Fly always!]&f"]
	quest.5A4C9F7F81D6B9DB.quest_subtitle: "胸甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.5A4C9F7F81D6B9DB.title: "&5重力调节附加&7单元&7[Gravitational Modulating Additional Unit]&f"
	quest.5AC68C8A4024F4C9.quest_desc: ["&a能量单元&7&r可用于所有&a&lMekaSuit部件&r,甚至&dMeka工具&r.\\n\\n我们可以在每个&e物品&r上添加8个.每个都会为&e物品&r增加更多&a能量储量&f&r.\\n\\n不,它不会增加物品中已有的&a能量&r.世上可没有免费的&a能量&r!\\n&7[Energy Units can be used in all the lMekaSuit Parts and even the Meka-Tool. \\n\\nWe can add 8 of them to each Item. Each adds more Energy Storage to the Item. \\n\\nNo, it doesn't increase the Energy that is already in it. There's no such thing as Free Energy!]&f"]
	quest.5AC68C8A4024F4C9.quest_subtitle: "万物&7[Everything]&f"
	quest.5AC68C8A4024F4C9.title: "&a能量&7单元&r&7[Energy Unit]&f"
	quest.5AEA705D6A64A982.quest_desc: ["如果你有一个主要用于生产&a钋&r的小型&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r,那么我们应该用它作为一个简单的故障保险!\\n\\n&a钋&r由&e&l&a太阳能中子活化器&f&r制造.你可能已经猜到它需要&e日光&r才能工作!\\n\\n所以,为了避免瓶颈(这在谈论&2&l反应堆&r时可能是致命的),我们可以在夜晚关闭&2&l反应堆&r!\\n\\n首先,将你的&2FRLA&r设置为激活模式.这会使&2&l反应堆&r在有&4&a红石信号&f&r时开启,没有时关闭.\\n\\n现在我们可以放置&e日光传感器&r并用&4红石&r将其连接到&2FRLA&r.\\n\\n然后,砰,就准备好了!\\n&7[If you have a small lFission Reactor primarily for Polonium then we should use this as a simple fail safe! \\n\\nPolonium is made with the lSolar Neutron Activator. You can probably tell it needs Daylight to work! \\n\\nSo, in order to stop bottle-necking (which can be deadly when we are talking about lReactors) we can turn off our lReactor when it is Nighttime! \\n\\nFirst, set your FRLA to Activation. This will turn on the lReactor when it has a Redstone Signal and turned off when it doesn't. \\n\\nNow we can place our Daylight Sensor and connect it to the FRLA with Redstone. \\n\\nThen, boom, it is ready!]&f"]
	quest.5AEA705D6A64A982.title: "时钟开关&7[Clock Switch]&f"
	quest.5B18676A77CD6069.quest_desc: ["让开,&b&lAE2&r和&3&lRS2&r!我们有&5&l&d通用机械&f&r了!\\n\\n&e&l量子物品编配&r(&e&lQIO&r)是一个虚拟&e物品&r存储系统.在我们使用它之前,需要一些&e物品&r来打开它并在其中存储&e物品&r!\\n\\n首先是系统的核心,&e&l&aQIO驱动器阵列&f&r.它是所有东西都会通过并连接的&5机器&r.\\n\\n它不需要&a能量&r,但像&a&l传送器&r和&5&l&a量子传送装置&f&r一样,它需要设置到一个网络!其他连接到&e&l&aQIO驱动器阵列&f&r的&e物品&r也需要设置到同一个网络.\\n\\n对于&e&aQIO驱动器&f&r,我们只需要将它们放入&e&l&aQIO驱动器阵列&f&r中!\\n&7[Move aside lAE2 and lRS2! We got lMekanism! \\n\\nThe lQuantum Item Orchestration (lQIO) is a Virtual Item storage. We'll need a few Items to open and store Items in it before we get to use it! \\n\\nFirst, is the heart of the system, the lQIO Drive Array. It is the Machine everything will go through and connect through. \\n\\nIt doesn't require Energy but like lTeleporters and lQuantum Entangloporters it will need to be set to a Network! The other Items that connect to the lQIO Drive Array will need to be set to that Network as well. \\n\\nFor the QIO Drives we just need to place them within the lQIO Drive Array! ]&f"]
	quest.5B18676A77CD6069.quest_subtitle: "(QIO)&7[(QIO)]&f"
	quest.5B18676A77CD6069.title: "&e&l量子物品编配&7[lQuantum Item Orchestration]&f"
	quest.5B9F3F32AB28A83A.quest_desc: ["&6&l&a热力锅炉&f&r 的内部和重要部分由特殊的方块构成!\\n\\n&6&a发热元件&f&r 负责将 &6热量&r 传递给 &9水&r,而 &9&a分压元件&f&r 则有助于产生蒸汽!\\n\\n如果我们建造更大的结构,可以在 &6&l锅炉&r 内部的不同方块之间留出空间,为蒸汽和 &9水&r 提供更多存储空间.\\n\\n顶部和 &9&a分压元件&f&r 之间的空气会增加蒸汽存储量.&9&a分压元件&f&r 和 &6&a发热元件&f&r 之间的空气则为 &9水&r 提供更多空间.\\n&7[The inside, and important part, of the lThermoelectric Boiler is made of fancy Blocks! \\n\\nSuperheating Elements which work in transferring Heat to Water and Pressure Dispersers which will help create the Steam! \\n\\nIf we use bigger Builds, we can leave room between the different Blocks inside the lBoiler to give more storage to Steam and Water. \\n\\nAir between the Top and the Pressure Dispersers will add to the Steam Storage. Air between the Pressure Dispersers and the Superheating Elements will give more room for Water.]&f"]
	quest.5B9F3F32AB28A83A.title: "&6&l&a热力锅炉&f 的热力部分&7[The Thermo part of the lThermoelectric Boiler]&f"
	quest.5CE7756D80E051CC.quest_desc: ["通常 &8&a灵魂沙&f&r 会减慢你的速度.通常是这样……\\n\\n装备 &8灵魂冲浪者 &7单元&r 后,你可以在 &8&a灵魂沙&f&r 和 &8泥土&r 上正常行走.\\n\\n装备更多此类单元后,你在 &8&a灵魂沙&f&r 和 &8泥土&r 上的行走速度甚至会比在其他方块上更快!\\n\\n嘿,也许 &8&a灵魂沙&f&r 小径不再是个坏主意了……\\n&7[Usually Soul Sand will slow you down. Usually... \\n\\nWith Soul Surfer Unit you will walk normally on Soul Sand and Soil. \\n\\nWith a few more you'll walk even faster on Soul Sand and Soil than on other Blocks! \\n\\nHey, maybe Soul Sand paths aren't a bad idea anymore...]&f"]
	quest.5CE7756D80E051CC.quest_subtitle: "靴子&7[Boots]&f"
	quest.5CE7756D80E051CC.title: "&8灵魂冲浪者 &7单元&7[Soul Surfer Unit]&f"
	quest.62B29AEF8468750E.quest_desc: ["等等,所以我们从 &6&a热源&f&r 承受更少的 &m伤害&r &a能量&r,并且还能从中产生 &a能量&r？算我一个!\\n\\n当你走在 &6岩浆块&f 上、穿过 &6火焰&f 或在 &6熔岩&r 中时,你的 &a&l&aMekaSuit裤子&f&r 会获得 &a能量&r.\\n\\n如果你的 &a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r 中装有 &a电荷分配 &7单元&r,它也会为其他 &a&lMekaSuit部件&r 充电.\\n&7[Wait, so we take less Damage Energy from Heat Sources and make Energy from them? Sign me up! \\n\\nWhen you walk on Magma, through Fire, or in Lava you'll gain Energy in your lMekaSuit Pants. \\n\\nIf you have Charge Distribution Unit in your lMekaSuit Bodyarmor, it will also Charge the other lMekaSuit Parts.]&f"]
	quest.62B29AEF8468750E.quest_subtitle: "裤子&7[Pants]&f"
	quest.62B29AEF8468750E.title: "&6&a地热发电机&f &7单元&7[Geothermal Generator Unit]&f"
	quest.63B0E39CA4B25A7E.quest_desc: ["&d&a营养糊剂&f&r 是通过 &d&l&a营养液化器&f&r 处理任何食用后可提供饥饿值的 &e物品&r 制成的.\\n\\n把它想象成一个巨型搅拌机!不过我不能保证 &d&a营养糊剂&f&r 的味道会很好……\\n\\n&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r 可以储存 &d营养糊剂&r,并且通过这个 &7单元&r,它会在你失去 &a饥饿值&f 时自动喂食你.\\n&7[Nutritional Paste is made from processing any Item that gives Food Bars when eaten through a lNutritional Liquifier. \\n\\nThink of it like a giant Blender! I can't promise the Nutritional Paste will taste good though... \\n\\nThe lMekaSuit Helmet can hold Nutrional Paste and with this Unit it will automatically feed you when you lose Hunger Points.]&f"]
	quest.63B0E39CA4B25A7E.quest_subtitle: "头盔&7[Helmet]&f"
	quest.63B0E39CA4B25A7E.title: "&d营养注射 &7单元&7[Nutritional Injection Unit]&f"
	quest.6518480251F0565A.quest_desc: ["等等,如果 Paxels 可以铺路、造耕地和剥树皮,为什么 &dMeka工具&r 不行!\\n\\n哦等等,如果你使用 &2农业 &7单元&r,它就可以.\\n\\n不过你需要启用配置中设置的选项.你不能用同一片草方块既造泥土又造耕地!\\n\\n我们不能将这个单元与 &7&a剪切单元&f&r 或 &5传送 &7单元&r 一起使用.\\n&7[Wait if Paxels can make Paths, make Farmland, and Strip Logs why can't the Meka-Tool! \\n\\nOh wait, it can if you just use the Farming Unit. \\n\\nYou'll need to enable which is set in the Configs though. You can't make Soil and Farmland from the same Grass! \\n\\nWe can't use this one with the Shearing Unit or Teleportation Unit.]&f"]
	quest.6518480251F0565A.quest_subtitle: "Meka工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.6518480251F0565A.title: "&2农业 &7单元&7[Farming Unit]&f"
	quest.67A9329C05F98633.quest_desc: ["说实话,如果你不需要更多 &a能量&r,并且希望你的 &2&l反应堆&r 尽可能安全,那就直接删除它!\\n\\n哦没错,你没听错!直接删除蒸汽!\\n\\n我知道在 &2&lMinecraft&r 中很多东西都很重要,通常最好保留它们,而不是扔掉……\\n\\n但蒸汽基本上只用于涡轮机产生 &a能量&r.\\n\\n不需要它？那就用管道把它输送到 &a终极垃圾桶&f 里!\\n&7[Honestly, if you don't need more Energy and would rather be as safe as you can with your lReactor then just delete it! \\n\\nOh yeah, you heard me! Just delete the Steam! \\n\\nI know lots of things are important in lMinecraft and it is usually greater to hold onto these, instead of tossing them... \\n\\nBut Steam is pretty much only for Turbines to make Energy. \\n\\nDon't need it? Then, Tube it into an Ultimate Trash Can!]&f"]
	quest.67A9329C05F98633.title: "扔掉它!&7[Toss it!]&f"
	quest.6A1174845810C7A1.quest_desc: ["&7&l&a改造站&f&r 是我们将 &7模块单元&r 安装到工具和盔甲中的方式.\\n\\n它需要 &a能量&r 才能运行,这当然是必须的.\\n\\n当你 &a右击&f 一个(已供能的)&7&l&a改造站&f&r 时,它会打开其 GUI.在这里我们可以看到包括盔甲和副手在内的整个物品栏.我们还有一个屏幕和 2 个额外槽位.\\n\\n这 2 个额外槽位分别用于放置我们的 &7模块单元&r(左侧槽位)和我们想要安装 &7模块单元&r 的盔甲或工具(右侧槽位).\\n\\n一旦两者都放入各自的槽位,它们会自动将 &7模块单元&r 安装到 &e物品&r 中.如果它们留在槽位中,我们可以在屏幕上查看 &e物品&r 中已安装的 &7模块单元&r.\\n\\n如果你想取出一个 &7模块单元&r,在屏幕上点击它,然后点击移除按钮.\\n\\n当我们安装了 &7模块单元&r 后,可以按下 (\\\\) 来调出它们的配置.在这里我们可以启用或禁用它们,以及更多功能!\\n&7[The lModification Station is how we will throw our Module Units into our Tools and Armor. \\n\\nIt will need Energy to operate, because of course it does. \\n\\nWhen you Right Click a (powered) lModification Station it will open up its GUI. Here we can see our entire Inventory including Armor and Offhand. We also have a Screen and 2 extra Slots. \\n\\nThe 2 extra Slots are where our Module Units (Left Slot) and our Armor or Tools we want to add the Module Units go (Right Slot). \\n\\nOnce both are added into their Slots, they will automatically place the Module Units into the Item. If they stay in the Slot, we can view the Module Units installed in the Item in the Screen. \\n\\nIf you want to take our a Module Unit, click it on the Screen, and then hit the Remove Button. \\n\\nWhen we have Module Units installed we can hit (\\\\\\) to pull up their Configs. Here we can Enable or Disable them, and more! ]&f"]
	quest.6A1174845810C7A1.title: "&l&7&a改造站&f&7[lModification Station]&f"
	quest.6B3BD54A34EB02C2.quest_desc: ["&a输导供应器&r 放置在 &a&l充能 &a输导矩阵&f&r 内,将增加其输入和输出的 &a能量&r 量.\\n\\n是的,它们的总量会相互叠加!\\n\\n&a基础输导供应器&r:每刻输入和输出 102.4kFE.\\n\\n&c高级输导供应器&r:每刻输入和输出 819.2kFE.\\n\\n&b&a精英输导供应器&f&r:每刻输入和输出 6.55MFE.\\n\\n&5&a终极输导供应器&f&r:每刻输入和输出 52.41MFE.\\n&7[Induction Providers are placed within the lEnergized Induction Matrix and will increase the amount of Energy it can Input and Output. \\n\\nAnd yes, their totals will stack on each other! \\n\\nBasic Induction Providers: will Input and Output 102.4kFE each Tick. \\n\\nAdvanced Induction Providers: will Input and Output 819.2kFE each Tick. \\n\\nElite Induction Providers: will Input and Output 6.55MFE each Tick. \\n\\nUltimate Induction Providers: will Input and Output 52.41MFE each Tick.]&f"]
	quest.6B3BD54A34EB02C2.quest_subtitle: "运输&7[Transport]&f"
	quest.6B3BD54A34EB02C2.title: "&a输导供应器&7[Induction Providers]&f"
	quest.6B7E13AB3BF2C5C8.quest_desc: [
		"&6&l&a热力锅炉&f&r 的建造方式与 &2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r 类似,外壳仅由外壳方块、玻璃和端口构成,而内部才是所有重要的东西!\\n\\n&6&l锅炉&r 的边缘需要是 &6&a锅炉外壳&f&r.屋顶和地板可以完全由 &6外壳方块&r 构成,或者中间部分可以用玻璃!\\n\\n墙壁类似,只是现在包括 &6锅炉端口&r.\\n\\n内部是我们的 &9&a分压元件&f&r 和 &6&a发热元件&f&r.\\n可以在天花板和 &9&a分压元件&f&r 之间留出空间,为蒸汽提供更多空间.\\n\\n我们也可以在 &9&a分压元件&f&r 下方和 &6&a发热元件&f&r 上方留出更多空间,为 &9水&r 提供更多空间.\\n&7[The lThermoelectric Boiler is built similar to the lFission Reactor with the outside shell being just Casings, Glass, and Ports, while the inside is all the important stuff! \\n\\nThe edges of the lBoiler will need to be Boiler Casings. The Roof and Floor can be made entirely of Casings or the middle can be made with Glass! \\n\\nThe Walls are similar, just now including Boiler Ports. \\n\\nThe inside is where our Pressure Dispersers and Superheating Elements. \\nThe Roof can be given space between the Ceiling and the Pressure Dispersers to give more room for Steam. \\n\\nWe can also give more space below the Pressure Dispersers and above the Superheating Elements to give more room for Water.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&6&l&a热力锅炉&f&r 本身不会做太多事情,它需要一些 &6端口&r 来输入我们的 &c化学品&f 和 &b流体&r 才能启动!\\n\\n现在我们将专注于冷却 &6&a过热钠&f&r!为此,我们需要在 &6&l锅炉&r 内放入 &6&a过热钠&f&r 和 &9水&r.\\n\\n一旦 &6&a过热钠&f&r 进入,&6&l锅炉&r 的 &6温度&r 将开始上升.在 &9水&r 的作用下,&6&a过热钠&f&r 会冷却下来,而 &9水&r 会沸腾成蒸汽.\\n\\n&6温度&r 越高,&9水&r 沸腾和 &6&a过热钠&f&r 冷却的速度就越快.如果我们想要/需要额外的 &6热量&r,可以通过 &6热力学导体&r 来 &6传导&r 一些.\\n\\n我们可以从 &6&a电阻型加热器&f&r 甚至 &2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r &6传导热量&r!\\n&7[The lThermoelectric Boiler won't do much on its own, it'll need some Ports moving our Chemicals and Fluids in to start it up! \\n\\nRight now we'll focus on cooling Superheated Sodium! For that we'll need Superheated Sodium and Water within the lBoiler. \\n\\nOnce the Superheated Sodium is in, the lBoiler's Temperature will start rising. With the Water the lSuperheated Sodium will cool down while the Water will boil into Steam. \\n\\nThe higher the Temperature the quicker Water will boil and Superheated Sodium will cool down. If we want/need extra Heat we can Conduct some via the Thermodynamic Conductors. \\n\\nWe can Conduct Heat from Resistive Heaters or even lFission Reactors!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这个多方块结构可以按照任何可用尺寸建造,不仅仅是图片中展示的尺寸.&a图片&f 仅仅展示了我们能建造的最小尺寸.\\n&7[This Multiblock can be made at any size available, not just what is shown through the Images. The Images merely show the smallest size we can make.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_boiler1.png width:100 height:75 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_boiler2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_boiler3.png width:110 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_boiler4.png width:100 height:110 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6B7E13AB3BF2C5C8.title: "&6&l&a热力锅炉&f&7[lThermoelectric Boiler]&f"
	quest.6C1F7A0B330B3F42.quest_desc: ["&a&lMekaSuit &f&m胸甲&r &a&l护甲&r,将是 &5难得素 &f&m护甲&r &5胸甲&r 的升级版.\\n\\n不过,升级它还需要一些其他 &e物品&r,比如 &d&a反物质靶丸&f&r、&a&a钋靶丸&f&r,甚至一个 &d&a终极输导元件&f&r!\\n\\n没有 &a能量&r 的 &a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r 表现得就像一件 &c&a下界合金胸甲&f&r.那么有 &a能量&r 时呢？它可能会阻挡所有 &a伤害&f(除了 &a魔法伤害&f),并且会消耗 &a能量&r 而不是 &a生命值&f!\\n\\n我们可以把它放入 &7&l&a改造站&f&r 来添加 &7模块单元&r 以升级它!&a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&r 拥有所有盔甲中最多的 &7模块单元&r,所以一定要看看它们!\\n&7[The lMekaSuit Chestplate lBodyarmor, will be an upgrade to 难得素 Bodyarmor Chestplate. \\n\\nIt will need a few other Items in order to upgrade it though, like an Antimatter Pellet, Polonium Pellets, and even an Ultimate Induction Cell! \\n\\nThe lMekaSuit Bodyarmor without Energy will act just like a Netherite Chestplate. What about with Energy? It might just block all Damage besides Magic Damage and will use Energy instead of Health! \\n\\nWe can toss it into a lModification Station in order to add Module Units which can upgrade it! The lMekaSuit Bodyarmor has the most Module Units of all the Armor, so definitely check them out!]&f"]
	quest.6C1F7A0B330B3F42.title: "&a&l&aMekaSuit护甲&f&7[lMekaSuit Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.6CCE920735187234.quest_desc: [
		"&9&l涡轮机&r 至少是一个 5x7x5 的 &5机器&r,但可以扩展以容纳更多蒸汽并产生更多 &a能量&r!\\n\\n&9&l涡轮机&r 的框架由 &9&a涡轮机外壳&f&r 构成.地板和天花板可以用 &9&a涡轮机外壳&f&r 或 &a结构玻璃&f 填充.\\n\\n在我们担心墙壁之前,先关注内部!那才是真正的赚钱机器!\\n\\n从地板算起的正中心是放置 &9转子&r 的地方.对于最小的涡轮机,我们需要 2 个!然后,在上面安装 &9叶片&r,总共 4 个.\\n\\n在最高的 &9转子&r 上方放置我们的 &9&a复杂旋钮装置&f&r,并用 &9&a分压元件&f&r 包围它.\\n\\n&9&a复杂旋钮装置&f&r 上方的一层是 &a电磁线圈&r,它们上方是我们的 &9&a饱和冷凝器&f&r.\\n\\n现在我们可以把 &9端口&r 和 &9通风口&r 放在墙壁上,其余部分用 &9&a涡轮机外壳&f&r 或 &a结构玻璃&f 填充!\\n&7[The lTurbine is atleast a 5x7x5 Machine but can be expanded to hold more Steam and make more Energy! \\n\\nThe frame of the lTurbine is made of Turbine Casings. The Floor and Ceiling can be filled in with Turbine Casings or Structural Glass. \\n\\nBefore we worry about the Walls let's focus on the inside! That's the real Money-maker! \\n\\nIn the dead center from the Floor is where our Rotors will be placed. For the smallest one we'll need 2! Then, attach the Blades on them, 4 in total. \\n\\nAbove the highest Rotor place our Rotational Complex and surround it with Pressure Dispersers. \\n\\nThe Layer above the Rotational Complex will be Electromagnetic Coils and above them will be our Saturating Condensers. \\n\\nNow we can put our Ports and Vents in our Walls and fill the rest with Turbine Casings or Structural Glass!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"幸运的是,&9&l涡轮机&r 使用起来比建造容易得多!\\n\\n通过 &9端口&r 用 &c管道&r 输入一些蒸汽,它就应该开始旋转了.它能容纳的蒸汽量由整个 &9&l涡轮机&r 结构的尺寸决定.\\n\\n然后,由于蒸汽在 &9&l涡轮机&r 中上升,&9转子&f 和 &9叶片&r 将开始旋转.这会带动 &9&a复杂旋钮装置&f&r,从而带动 &a电磁线圈&r 产生 &a能量&r!\\n\\n&a能量&r 可以通过我们的第二个 &9端口&r 用 &a线缆&r 输出.&a能量&r 的产量取决于 &9转子&f 和 &9叶片&r 的旋转速度.而这本身又取决于输入 &9&l涡轮机&r 的蒸汽量.\\n\\n如果我们使用 &9&a饱和冷凝器&f&r,我们可以从蒸汽中回收一点 &9水&r.我们可以从 &9通风口&r 取出这些 &9水&r,并送回我们的 &2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r!\\n\\n我们的 &9&l涡轮机&r GUI 中有一个设置,类似于 &9&l&a电解分离器&f&r 中的设置.我们可以选择”丢弃多余蒸汽\\n&7[Thankfully the lTurbine is much easier to use than Build! \\n\\nTube in some Steam through the Port and it should start spinning. The amount of Steam it can hold is determined by the size of the entire lTurbine Build. \\n\\nThen the Rotors and Blades will start spinning because of the Steam rising through the lTurbine. This will move the Rotational Complex which moves the Electromagnetic Coils making Energy! \\n\\nThe Energy can be Cabled out of our 2nd Port. The amount of Energy is determined on how fast the Rotors and Blades are moving. Which itself is determined on how much Steam is Input into the lTurbine. \\n\\nIf we use Saturating Condensers we'll get a little Water back from our Steam. We can take this Water out from the Vents and back into our lFission Reactor! \\n\\nWe do have a setting within our lTurbine GUI which is similar to those within the lElectrolytic Separator. We can choose to Dump Excess Steam, to constantly have it working at fastest Energy production. We can Dump Steam, incase you want to get rid of it I guess... or Idle which is default! If you use one that isn't Idle, it won't recycle Water from Steam.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这个多方块结构可以按照任何可用尺寸建造,不仅仅是图片中展示的尺寸.&a图片&f 仅仅展示了我们能建造的最小尺寸.\\n&7[This Multiblock can be made at any size available, not just what is shown through the Images. The Images merely show the smallest size we can make.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine3.png width:110 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine5.png width:100 height:110 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine6.png width:100 height:120 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_turbine7.png width:100 height:125 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6CCE920735187234.title: "&9&l涡轮机&7[lTurbine]&f"
	quest.6D7D0A5313284B53.quest_desc: ["嘿,不错的鞋子!&a&l&aMekaSuit靴子&f&r 是 &5&a难得素靴子&f&r 的升级版.\\n\\n不,不仅仅是 &5&a难得素靴子&f&r,你还需要一个 &d&a反物质靶丸&f&r、&a&a钋靶丸&f&r 和一个 &d&a终极输导元件&f&r!\\n\\n你真的在乎靴子的属性吗？谁会打你的脚!哦对了,&a摔落伤害&f 忘了.\\n\\n嗯,如果它没有充能,它的保护量就和 &c&a下界合金靴子&f&r 一样……但如果充能了,它会使用 &a能量&r 来保护你.\\n\\n&7&l&a改造站&f&r 是一个 &5机器&r,我们可以用它来添加 &7模块单元&r 以升级我们的 &a&lMekaSuit部件&r,包括 &a&l靴子&r.这些升级类似于许多附魔!\\n&7[Hey, nice Kicks! The lMekaSuit Boots are an upgrade to 难得素 Boots. \\n\\nNo, not just 难得素 Boots, you'll also need an Antimatter Pellet, Polonium Pellets, and an Ultimate Induction Cell! \\n\\nDo you really care about the stats of Boots? Who's hitting your Feet! Oh yeah Fall Damage forgot. \\n\\nWell if it isn't charged it will protect the same amount as Netherite Boots... but if it is Charged it will use Energy to protect you. \\n\\nlModification Station is a Machine we can use to add Module Units to upgrade our lMekaSuit Parts, including lBoots. These upgrades are similar to lots of Enchants!]&f"]
	quest.6D7D0A5313284B53.title: "&a&l&aMekaSuit靴子&f&7[lMekaSuit Boots]&f"
	quest.71766BD7321FCB13.quest_desc: ["太好了,又一个&c&l&a化学灌注器&f&r!\\n\\n将&a&a氧化铀&f&r和&7氢氟酸&r结合以制造&a&a六氟化铀&f&r.\\n\\n现在我们可以通过&5&l&a同位素离心机&f&r处理&a&a六氟化铀&f&r,最终得到我们美丽的&2&a裂变燃料&f&r.\\n&7[Great, another lChemical Infuser! \\n\\nCombine the Uranium Oxide and Hydrofluorite Acid to create Uranium Hexafluoride. \\n\\nNow we can process the Uranium Hexafluoride through an lIsotopic Centrifuge to finally get our beautiful Fissile Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.71766BD7321FCB13.title: "&2&a裂变燃料&f&7[Fissile Fuel]&f"
	quest.7177653B736AB10E.quest_desc: ["我们可以在&c&l&a化学灌注器&f&r中结合&c氘&r和&a氚&r来制造我们的&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r.我们也可以直接将两种&c化学品&r&c传输&r到&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r中,并在&c&l反应堆&r内结合它们.\\n\\n如果我们只&c传输&r&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r,它会以传输的速率注入.但如果我们&c传输&r&c氘&r和&a氚&r并在&c&l反应堆&r内结合,我们可以选择任何我们想要的注入速率!\\n\\n我们还需要一点&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r放入&e黑体辐射腔&r中,并将其放入&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r中进行初始启动.\\n\\n你问怎么制造&e黑体辐射腔&r？只需在&9&l&a冶金灌注机&f&r中用10mb的&0碳&r&9灌注&r&f4个&e&a金粉&f&r来合成&e黑体辐射腔&r.\\n\\n哦等等,它出来是空的,把它扔进一个有&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r的&5机器&r里填满.然后,把它放进&c&l&a湮灭反应堆&f&r的GUI槽位中,就准备好了!\\n&7[We can combine Deuterium and Tritium in a lChemical Infuser to make our D-T Fuel. We can also just Port both the Chemicals into the lFusion Reactor and combine them within the lReactor. \\n\\nIf we just Port D-T Fuel it will Inject at the rate it is Ported into. But if we Port both Deuterium and Tritium and combine it within the lReactor we can pick any Inject Rate we want! \\n\\nWe'll also need a little dab of D-T Fuel within a Hohlraum and put that within the lFusion Reactor for the initial start up. \\n\\nHow do we make a Hohlraum you ask? Just Infuse 4 Gold Dust with 10mb of Carbon within a lMetallurgic Infuser to Craft the Hohlraum. \\n\\nOh wait it comes out empty, throw it into a Machine that has D-T Fuel to fill it up. Then, put it within the Slot in the lFusion Reactor's GUI, and it is ready!]&f"]
	quest.7177653B736AB10E.title: "&5&a氘氚燃料&f&r&7[D-T Fuel]&f"
	quest.7310BBC4A90EDA9D.quest_desc: ["&e&a便携式QIO仪表板&f&r允许我们从任何地方查看我们的&e&lQIO系统&r!\\n\\n&a右击&f这个&e物品&r使其属于你!\\n\\n现在你可以&a右击&f它,并为我们的&e&lQIO系统&r设置一个网络频率.\\n\\n砰,&e&aQIO仪表板&f&r能做的所有事情,我们都能用这个小家伙做到!\\n&7[The Portable QIO Dashboard allows us to view our lQIO System from anywhere! \\n\\nRight Click with the Item to make it yours! \\n\\nNow you can Right Click it and set a Network Frequency to our lQIO System. \\n\\nBoom everything the QIO Dashboard does, we can do with this little friend!]&f"]
	quest.7310BBC4A90EDA9D.title: "&e&a便携式QIO仪表板&f&7[Portable QIO Dashboard]&f"
	quest.77B6A7151B3E5980.quest_desc: ["&a&a连锁采掘&f&r 是有限制的 FTB Ultimine.\\n\\n当我们开采矿石或原木时,与其相连的同种方块也会被一并破坏.\\n\\n节省大量时间……但我们也有 FTB Ultimine……所以.\\n&7[Vein Mining is a limited FTB Ultimine. \\n\\nWhen we Mine Ores or Logs, the same Blocks connected to it will be broken with it. \\n\\nSaving lots of time... but we also have FTB Ultimine... so. ]&f"]
	quest.77B6A7151B3E5980.quest_subtitle: "通用机械工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.77B6A7151B3E5980.title: "&a&a连锁采掘&f &7单元&7[Vein Mining Unit]&f"
	quest.7846B7FFC3DD85C5.quest_desc: ["&d&l超临界&a相移&fe&r (&d&lS.P.S.&r) 会将我们的 &a钋&r 转化为 &d反物质&r.\\n\\n为此,我们需要 &a钋&r、&a能量&r、一个混合两者的地方,以及一个取出 &d反物质&r 的地方!\\n\\n所以我们需要为每样东西准备一个 &d端口&r!\\n两侧各 1 个 &d端口&r 用于输入 &a能量&r,1 个 &d端口&r 用于向 &d&lSPS&r 提供 &a钋&r,最后一个用于取出我们的 &d反物质&r.\\n&7[The lSuper-Critical Phase Shifter (lS.P.S.) will turn our Polonium into Antimatter. \\n\\nIn order to do that, we'll need Polonium, Energy, a place to mix both, and a place to take Antimatter out! \\n\\nSo we'll need a Port for each of those! \\n2 Ports for Energy at the sides, 1 Port for giving the lSPS Polonium, and the last for taking our Antimatter out.]&f"]
	quest.7846B7FFC3DD85C5.title: "&d&a超临界移相器端口&f&7[SPS Ports]&f"
	quest.7864C8F2CBC910CB.quest_desc: ["&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r,顾名思义,就是戴在头上的部件!你需要一个 &d&a反物质靶丸&f&r、一个 &a&a钋靶丸&f&r、一个 &d&a终极输导元件&f&r,以及更多!\\n\\n它是 &5&a难得素头盔&f&r 的升级版.虽然它的 &a护甲值&f 低得多,但它的运作方式与 &5&a难得素头盔&f&r 不同.\\n\\n如果 &a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r 未充能,它的属性将与 &c&a下界合金头盔&f&r 类似,但有趣的部分来了!&a&lMekaSuit头盔&r 会阻挡所有 &a伤害&f(但 &a魔法伤害&f 除外)并消耗 &a能量&r.\\n\\n此外,穿戴时,它会在我们的 HUD 上显示:我们的坐标、&a&lMekaSuit&r 内的 &a能量&r,并将 &a护甲值&f 替换为 &a能量条&r.\\n\\n我们可以使用 &7&l&a改造站&f&r 为 &a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&r 添加升级,例如增加 &a能量&r 以承受更少的 &a伤害&f!&a水下呼吸&f、免受 &a辐射&r 伤害,甚至 &e太阳能充电&r!\\n&7[The lMekaSuit Helmet, is obviously the part that goes on your head! You'll need an Antimatter Pellet, Polonium Pellets, an Ultimate Induction Cell, and more! \\n\\nIt serves as an Upgrade to 难得素 Helmets. While it has a lot less Armor Points, it works different from 难得素 Helmets. \\n\\nIf the lMekaSuit Helmet isn't Charged, it will work with similar stats to a Netherite Helmet, but here's the fun part! lMekaSuits Helmets will block all Damage (but Magic Damage) and use up Energy. \\n\\nAlso when worn, it will display on our HUD: our Coordinates, Energy within our lMekaSuit, and will replace the Armor Points with an Energy Bar. \\n\\nWe can use the lModification Station to give Upgrades to the lMekaSuit Helmet, like more Energy to take even less Damage! Water Breathing, safety from Radiation, and even Solar Charging!]&f"]
	quest.7864C8F2CBC910CB.title: "&a&l&aMekaSuit头盔&f&7[lMekaSuit Helmet]&f"
	quest.795B80BF12D23897.quest_desc: ["顾名思义,但由于它是宝藏附魔,并非所有人都知道它.\\n\\n当穿着附有 &a冰霜行者&f 的靴子或装有 &b&a冰霜行者&f &7单元&r 的 &a&l&aMekaSuit靴子&f&r 走过 &9水&r 时,&9水&r 会变成 &b冰&r!\\n\\n不过 &b冰&r 不会永久存在,它很快就会融化!\\n\\n&a冰霜行者&f 等级越高,生成的 &b冰&r 越多!\\n&7[It is in the name, but it being a Treasure Enchantment not everyone will know about it. \\n\\nWhen walking over Water with Boots enchanted with Frost Walker or lMekaSuit Boots with the Frost Walker Units the Water will turn into Ice! \\n\\nThe Ice won't last forever though, it will thaw out shortly! \\n\\nThe more Frost Walker, the more Ice!]&f"]
	quest.795B80BF12D23897.quest_subtitle: "靴子&7[Boots]&f"
	quest.795B80BF12D23897.title: "&b&a冰霜行者&f &7单元&7[Frost Walker Unit]&f"
	quest.7B0764DDE94E73D0.quest_desc: ["In bigger lReactors we'll need a more advanced fail safe. \\nFor this one, our lReactor will need to be atleast 5 Blocks wide. That gives 3 Block width for our 2 FRLA. \\n\\nPlace 1 of our FRLA in the lReactor and set it to either High Temperature or Damage Critical. Then, place the second one atleast 1 Block away while on the same Y Level. The second will need to be set to Activation. \\n\\nNow, let's do some Redstone! \\n\\nPlace a Redstone Repeater facing out from the first FRLA. Then, where the Repeater is facing, place a Block that can transmit Redstone. \\n\\nOn that Block, place a Redstone Torch in the direction that the second FRLA is. \\n\\nAfter that, place Redstone Dust next to the Torch, while on the same X/Z Level of the second FRLA. And lastly, place a second Redstone Repeater going from the Redstone Dust and into the second FRLA."]
	quest.7B0764DDE94E73D0.title: "高级故障保险&7[Advanced Fail Safe]&f"
	quest.7B385FD1CBE02C85.quest_desc: ["如果我们使用 &9水&r 作为 &b冷却剂&r,我们会得到蒸汽作为副产品!\\n\\n现在我们用它做什么呢？\\n&7[If we are using Water as a Coolant, we will get Steam as a byproduct! \\n\\nNow what do we do with it?]&f"]
	quest.7B385FD1CBE02C85.title: "蒸汽&7[Steam]&f"
	quest.7C7BD54624ED9AC2.quest_desc: ["字面意思就是创造模式飞行.\\n\\n你不能将此功能与 &c喷气背包 &7单元&r 同时使用,并且飞行会消耗 &a能量&r!\\n\\n在其配置中,你还可以提高飞行速度.\\n&7[Literally just Creative Flight. \\n\\nYou can't use this with the Jetpack Unit and yes it will use Energy to Fly! \\n\\nWithin its Configs you can increase how fast you Fly as well.]&f"]
	quest.7C7BD54624ED9AC2.quest_subtitle: "胸甲&7[Bodyarmor]&f"
	quest.7C7BD54624ED9AC2.title: "&d重力调节 &7单元&7[Gravitational Modulating Unit]&f"
	quest.7D279FC39DA5C630.quest_desc: ["我们的 &c&a三氧化硫&f&r 还没处理完!不过我们需要一些 &a水蒸气&f 来进一步加工它.\\n\\n要获得 &a水蒸气&f,我们可以使用 &c&l旋转 &b冷凝器&r 将 &9水&r 转化为 &a水蒸气&f!\\n更多 &c灌注&r!将我们的 &a水蒸气&f 与 &c三氧化硫&r 结合,制成 &a&a硫酸&f&r.\\n\\n嗯,现在是酸了……但不是我们想要的那种……\\n\\n哦对了,我们需要 &d萤石&r,可以通过采矿获得.然后,使用 &3&l&a化学溶解室&f&r 用 &d萤石&r 稀释 &a&a硫酸&f&r,最终得到我们的 &7&a氢氟酸&f&r!\\n&7[We aren't done with our Sulfur Trioxide yet! We will need some Water Vapor to process it further though. \\n\\nTo get Water Vapor we can use the lRotary Condensator to turn Water into Water Vapor! \\nMore Infusing! Combine our Water Vapor with our Sulfuric Trioxide to make Sulfuric Acid. \\n\\nWell it's an Acid now... but not the right one... \\n\\nOh yeah, we'll need Fluorite which we can get from Mining Ores. Then, use the lChemical Dissolution Chamber to dilute the Sulfuric Acid with Fluorite to finally get our Hydrofluoric Acid!]&f"]
	quest.7D279FC39DA5C630.title: "&c&a三氧化硫&f&r 转化为 &7&a氢氟酸&f&7[Sulfur Trioxide into Hydrofluoric Acid]&f"
	quest.7E3C84D7FCEC9D52.quest_desc: [
		"我们能制造的最小(可工作的)&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r 是 3x4x3.\\n\\n底座和框架需要用 &2&a裂变反应堆外壳&f&r 制成,而内部需要是空的,或者放置 &2&a燃料棒&f 组件&r 或 &2&a控制棒组件&f&r!\\n\\n墙壁内侧(非边缘)可以放置我们的 &2&a裂变反应堆端口&f&r 或 &2FRLA&r,其余部分可以用 &2&a反应堆玻璃&f&r 填充.\\n\\n一旦我们的 &2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r 建成,我们可以 &a右击&f &2反应堆&r 上任意位置(除了 &2FRLA&r)来打开其 GUI.\\n&7[The smallest (working) lFission Reactor we can make is 3x4x3. \\n\\nThe base and frame will need to be made of Fission Reactor Casing while the inside will need to be either Empty, or have Fuel Rod Assembly or Control Rod Assembly! \\n\\nThe inside of the walls (not the edges) can have our Fission Reactor Ports or FRLA and the rest can be filled with Reactor Glass. \\n\\nOnce our lFission Reactor is built, we can Right Click anywhere (besides the FRLA) on the Reactor to open its GUI. ]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"This can look pretty scary to new Players so we'll go through it slowly to understand it better! \\n\\nAt the top, we can see 4 different Bars. These are where we can see how much Fissile Fuel, Coolant, Heated Coolant, and Nuclear Waste. \\n\\nBetween the Bars we'll find the main menu of the lReactor. It will tell us whether it is on or off, how Fissile Fuel is being used up every Tick, how much Temperature it rises every Tick, and how much Damage the lReactor has suffered! \\n\\nBelow all of these we'll see 2 Buttons! One to turn on the lReactor saying Activate and the other to turn it off saying SCRAM. Next to the SCRAM Button is a little image to help Players know if it is on or off. Green when on, Red when off. \\n\\nBelow those Buttons we'll see how Hot our lReactor is and below it will show a visual of the Temperature change. "
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"在此菜单之外,我们可以点击顶部标签页调出统计信息.\\n\\n顶部图表显示了在发生 &a损伤&f 前可以容纳多少热量,&2燃料&r 在 &2&l反应堆&r 内有多少空间,以及它利用热量消耗 &2燃料&r 的效率如何.\\n\\n其余部分都基于每游戏刻可以使用多少 &2燃料&r.我们可以在类型框中设置最大值.单位也是每游戏刻毫桶!\\n\\n我们可以在主菜单侧面找到的另一个标签页是关于温度的!\\n\\n它会显示其散热率以及显示的温度单位.我们可以通过点击标签页来更改温度单位.你很可能使用 F(华氏度)或 C(摄氏度),但我们也可以使用 K(开尔文)、R(兰金度)或 STP(标准温度和压力)!\\n&7[Outside of this menu, we can Click the Top Tab to pull up the Statistics. \\n\\nThe top Chart shows off how much Heat can be held until Damage occurs, how much room Fuel has within the lReactor, and how Efficient it is at using Heat to use up Fuel. \\n\\nThe rest is all based on how much Fuel can be used each Tick. We can set a max in the Type Box. It is also set at mB per Tick! \\n\\nThe other Tab we can find on the side of the main menu is for our Temperature! \\n\\nIt will show its Dissipiation rate as well as the Temperature Unit shown. We can change the Temperature Unit by Clicking on the Tab. You'll most likely use F (Fahrenheit) or C (Celsius) but we can also use K (Kelvin), R (Rankine), or STP (Standard Temperature and Pressure)!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"熔毁!\\n\\n如果 &a损伤&f 达到 250%,&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&r 将会爆炸.爆炸时会破坏方块、引发火灾,最糟糕的是……扩散 &a辐射&r!\\n\\n让我们避免这种情况!\\n\\n当温度超过 1,200K 时,&a损耗&f 会增加.我们需要使用 &b冷却剂&r 来降低温度.\\n\\n确保它有持续的 &b冷却剂&r 供应,并确保 &b冷却剂输出&r 不会形成瓶颈.如果发生这种情况,将无法使用更多的 &b冷却剂&r,温度将会升高.\\n\\n泄漏!\\n\\n如果 &8&a核废料&f&r 条已满,也可能发生 &a辐射&r 泄漏.这会在 &2&l反应堆&r 周围扩散 &a辐射&r.通过持续移除 &8&a核废料&f&r 甚至使用 &2FRLA&r 来了解 &8废料&r 何时已满,以避免这种情况!\\n&7[MELTDOWNS! \\n\\nThe lFission Reactor will explode if it goes to 250% Damage. When it explodes it will break Blocks, start Fires, and worst of all... spread Radiation! \\n\\nLet's avoid that! \\n\\nThe Damage will increase when the Temperature goes over 1,200K. We'll need to use Coolants to keep that Temperature down. \\n\\nMake sure it has a constant supply of Coolant and make sure the Coolant Output doesn't bottle-neck. If this happens, more Coolant can't be used and the Temperature will increase. \\n\\nLEAKS! \\n\\nRadiation leaks can also occur if the Nuclear Waste Bar is full. This will spread Radiation around the lReactor. Avoid this with constantly removing Nuclear Waste and even using FRLA to know when Waste is full!]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这个多方块结构可以制作成任何可用尺寸,不仅仅是图片中显示的尺寸.&a图片&f 仅仅展示了我们能制作的最小尺寸.\\n&7[This Multiblock can be made at any size available, not just what is shown through the Images. The Images merely show the smallest size we can make.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fission1.png width:100 height:75 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fission2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fission3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/mek/mek_fission4.png width:100 height:110 align:center}"
	]
	quest.7E3C84D7FCEC9D52.quest_subtitle: "将 1 个元素分裂为 2 个&7[Splitting 1 Element into 2]&f"
	quest.7E3C84D7FCEC9D52.title: "&2&l&a裂变反应堆&f&7[lFission Reactor]&f"
	quest.7ECE00D12CFC50A4.quest_desc: ["&b&a精准采集&f&7单元&r 将作为 &dMeka-Tool&r 的 &a精准采集附魔&f.\\n\\n但不仅仅是镐的部分,还包括 &dMeka-Tool&r 内的铲子和其他工具!\\n\\n所以你可以采集石头和矿石,以及草方块和菌丝体.\\n\\n我们不能在 &dMeka-Tool&r 上同时使用此 &7单元&r 和 &d&a矿石提炼&f &7单元&r.\\n&7[The Silk Touch Unit will act as a Silk Touch Enchantment for the Meka-Tool. \\n\\nBut not just the Pickaxe part, also the Shovel and other Tools within the Meka-Tool! \\n\\nSo you can pick up Stone and Ores plus Grass and Mycelium. \\n\\nWe can't use this Unit with the Ore Refinement Unit on a Meka-Tool.]&f"]
	quest.7ECE00D12CFC50A4.quest_subtitle: "通用机械工具&7[Meka-Tool]&f"
	quest.7ECE00D12CFC50A4.title: "&b&a精准采集&f&7单元&7[Silk Touch Unit]&f"
	task.11151860F09B78E1.title: "&e&aQIO驱动器&f&7[QIO Drives]&f"
	task.151AF2F49AAEBBDA.title: "&a感应单元&7[Induction Cells]&f"
	task.363BADA865C39474.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.496C4FDD2515EB24.title: "&a感应供应器&7[Induction Providers]&f"
	task.59F0226D83026397.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.00C95A190BE2CBF9.quest_desc: ["要获得 &#994ABA苯乙烯&r,你必须让 &#C2C969&a铁粉&f&r 与 &#69C9B6乙苯&r 和蒸汽反应.&#69C9B6乙苯&r 是蒸馏 &#CDCF95蒸汽裂化石脑油&r 的产物.\\n&7[To obtain &#994ABAStyrene, you must react &#C2C969Iron Dust with &#69C9B6EthylBenzene and Steam. &#69C9B6EthylBenzene is the product of distilling &#CDCF95Steam Cracked Naptha.]&f"]
	quest.00C95A190BE2CBF9.title: "高级蒸馏&7[Advanced Distillation]&f"
	quest.011B8BD02D80DDD4.quest_desc: ["你可以在世界各地轻松找到 &#6E2D6E&a钨矿石&f&r.破坏它会掉落 &#A140A1&a粗钨&f&r.\\n&7[You can find &#6E2D6ETungsten Ore around the world easily. Breaking it will yield &#A140A1Raw Tungsten.]&f"]
	quest.024BD22824C7F53A.quest_desc: ["蒸馏 &#F0C87D蒸汽裂化石脑油&r 会给我们 &#8FD5E3甲苯&r.\\n&7[Distilling &#F0C87DSteam-Cracked Naptha will give us &#8FD5E3Toluene.]&f"]
	quest.0B60DA8F65E5DF06.quest_desc: ["你可以通过多种方式之一粉碎 &#A140A1&a粗钨&f&r 以获得 &#C452C4&a钨粉&f&r.\\n&7[You can crush down the &#A140A1Raw Tungsten in one of many ways to get &#C452C4Tungsten Dust.]&f"]
	quest.0C229BE9B57269EF.quest_desc: ["&#EBA844&a坎塔尔合金粉&f&r 必须在 &#816DF7&a电力高炉&f&r 中熔炼.\\n&7[&#EBA844Kanthal Dust must be smelted in an &#816DF7Electric Blast Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.0CD36928116E868E.quest_desc: ["&#F783F3&a氯乙烯&f&r 可以与 &#9683F7&a小撮铅粉&f&r 或 &#FEA8FF铬 &a小撮粉末&f&r 混合,得到 &#F36EF5聚&a氯乙烯&f&r.\\n&7[&#F783F3Vinyl Chloride can be mixed with either &#9683F7Lead Tiny Dust or &#FEA8FFChromium Tiny Dust to get &#F36EF5PolyVinyl Chloride.]&f"]
	quest.0EA327E405EDFF02.quest_desc: ["&#9C6C35乙炔&r 与 &#DEAB6D盐酸&r 混合会得到 &#F783F3&a氯乙烯&f&r.\\n&7[&#9C6C35Acetylene mixed with &#DEAB6DHydroChloric Acid will give you &#F783F3Vinyl Chloride.]&f"]
	quest.1A83615B7E1D3540.quest_desc: ["将 &9水&r 放入带有燃料的 &#45BF56反应堆&r 中会产生 &#8F49C4氘&r.还有其他方法可以获得它,但 &#45BF56反应堆&r 提供了可能的最快方式.\\n&7[Putting Water into a &#45BF56Reactor with fuel will yield us &#8F49C4Deuterium. There are other ways to get this as well but &#45BF56Reactors provide the fastest way possible.]&f"]
	quest.226187AA3F1B6DB1.quest_desc: ["将 &#D4C35D沙子&r、&8燧石&r、&#8DF0EE氮气&r 和 &#69C9C7甲苯&r 混合在一起,会得到 &#D66D40&a工业TNT&f&r.\\n&7[Mixing together &#D4C35DSand, Flint, &#8DF0EENitrogen and &#69C9C7Toluene will give us &#D66D40Industrial TNT.]&f"]
	quest.22B8D57337944D9C.quest_desc: ["&#DF9DE0&a热钛锭&f&r现在可以在&#5CD1CF&a真空冷冻机&f&r中冷却,以获得可用的&#F069F0&a钛锭&f&r.\\n&7[&#DF9DE0Titanium Hot Ingots can now be cooled down in the &#5CD1CFVacuum Freezer to get usable &#F069F0Titanium Ingots.]&f"]
	quest.22B8D57337944D9C.title: "&#F069F0&a钛锭&f&7[&#F069F0Titanium Ingot]&f"
	quest.23DB52ECA259F36D.quest_desc: [
		"&#45BF56反应堆&r中的&a重水&f产生&#EB5266氚&r和&#C09EDE&a重水蒸汽&f&r.\\n&7[Heavy Water in a &#45BF56Reactor produces &#EB5266Tritium and &#C09EDEHeavy Water Steam.]&f"
		""
		"&#EB5266氚&r用于高级组件,而&#C09EDE&a重水蒸汽&f&r可以在&#DEAB47&a热交换器&f&r中回收成&#8C47C9&a重水&f&r.\\n&7[The &#EB5266Tritium is used for advanced components whereas the &#C09EDEHeavy Water Steam can be recycled into &#8C47C9Heavy Water in a &#DEAB47Heat Exchanger.]&f"
	]
	quest.267A357B28228694.quest_desc: ["&#4DB85E&a随机存取存储器&f&r在&#5EC7E6&a化学反应器&f&r中用&#A1A1A1&a丁苯橡胶&f&r、&#D15EE6氩&r、&7&a锑粉&f&r、&#5ED2E6&a铝粉&f&r和&#5D76C2&a硅片&f&r制造.\\n&7[&#4DB85ERandom Access Memory is made in a &#5EC7E6Chemical Reactor with &#A1A1A1Styrene-Butadiene Rubber, &#D15EE6Argon, Antimony Dust, &#5ED2E6Aluminum Dust and &#5D76C2Silicon Wafers.]&f"]
	quest.282A23C3E7561796.quest_desc: [
		"&#94C0E3&a处理阵列&f&r是一个大型多方块结构,允许你模拟并行运行的机器.最大并行操作数为&#94E3A264&r.\\n&7[The &#94C0E3Processing Array is a large multiblock that allows you to simulate machines running in parallel. Maximum parallel operations are &#94E3A264.]&f"
		""
		"要建造这个多方块结构,首先在控制器方块的GUI中选择你想要模拟的并行机器数量.\\n&7[To build the multiblock, firstly select the amount of parallel machines you wish to simulate in the GUI of the controller block.]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/modernindustrialization/proc_array_gui.png width:175 height:100 align:center}"
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"要使用这台机器,你需要将想要模拟的机器放入GUI右侧的槽位.你需要与操作数相同数量的机器.\\n&7[To use the machine, you need to put the machine you want to simulate into the slot on the right side of GUI. You need the same amount of machines as you want operations.]&f"
		""
		"此外,&#94C0E3&a处理阵列&f&r通常也接受所有升级.\\n&7[Also, &#94C0E3Processing Array accepts normally all the upgrades as well.]&f"
	]
	quest.2A95F4F998835B43.quest_subtitle: "9个粒 -> &a1个锭&f&7[9 Nuggets -> 1 Ingot]&f"
	quest.3003598CE8B1FAAA.quest_subtitle: "更好的技术&7[Better Technology]&f"
	quest.3003598CE8B1FAAA.title: "更高级的组件&7[More Advanced Components]&f"
	quest.31CB278B4BA7B25E.quest_desc: ["离心&#B5E7F7&a液态空气&f&r会给你3种输出:&#A5CAD9氧&r、&#78ADC2氮&r和&#DD91ED氩&r.我们将在不久的将来使用这种&#DD91ED氩&r.\\n&7[Centrifuging &#B5E7F7Liquid Air will give you 3 outputs: &#A5CAD9Oxygen, &#78ADC2Nitrogen and &#DD91EDArgon. We will use this &#DD91EDArgon in the near future.]&f"]
	quest.31CB278B4BA7B25E.quest_subtitle: "这很合理&7[It makes sense]&f"
	quest.31CB278B4BA7B25E.title: "离心空气&7[Centrifuging Air]&f"
	quest.352A226915809E1B.quest_desc: ["现在,&#A57DE3打包机&r将允许我们将&#7DD2E3不锈钢&r、&#B37DE3钨&r和&#E37DDB&a钛锭&f&r组合成新的&#3946E3混合抗爆合金锭&r.\\n&7[The &#A57DE3Packer will now allow us to combine &#7DD2E3Stainless Steel, &#B37DE3Tungsten and &#E37DDBTitanium Ingot into a new &#3946E3Mixed Blastproof Ingot. ]&f"]
	quest.35FDC436DE07635F.quest_desc: ["&#DB62DE&a聚爆压缩机&f&r利用爆炸的力量来组合资源.它可以用来获得更高效的&#8762DE混合&a抗爆合金锭&f&r以及许多其他有用的资源.\\n&7[The &#DB62DEImplosion Compressor uses the power of explosives to combine resources. It can be used to get more efficient &#8762DEMixed Blastproof Alloy Ingots as well as many more useful resources.]&f"]
	quest.3601DD545E1D11B4.quest_desc: [
		"&#DD91ED氩气&r与&#83729E&a硅粉&f&r和&#AAA0BA&a小撮铱粉&f&r反应,将得到&#919191&a单晶硅&f&r.\\n&7[&#DD91EDArgon reacting with &#83729ESilicon Dust and &#AAA0BAIridium Tiny Dust will give us &#919191Monocrystalline Silicon.]&f"
		""
		"&#AAA0BA铱&r在主世界以矿石形式存在.\\n&7[&#AAA0BAIridium is found as an ore in the overworld.]&f"
	]
	quest.36D35C35BBC0A555.quest_subtitle: "最高效的一种&7[The most efficient one]&f"
	quest.386ABEB4249D157D.quest_desc: ["一块&#919191&a单晶硅&f&r可以被切割成32片&#8FA4B5&a硅片&f&r.\\n&7[A singular &#919191Monocrystalline Silicon can be cut into 32 &#8FA4B5Silicon Wafers.]&f"]
	quest.3891F8D4201E6BFD.quest_desc: [
		"&#EBA844&a坎塔尔合金锭&f&r可以加工成细线,然后塑造成电缆,最终制成&#EBA844坎塔尔线圈&r.\\n&7[The &#EBA844Kanthal Ingot can be processed into Fine Wire, which can be molded into Cable to finally make the &#EBA844Kanthal Coils. ]&f"
		""
		"&#EBA844坎塔尔线圈&r能让我们的&#816DF7&a电力高炉&f&r在更高的&#F76D6D温度&r下运行,从而解锁更多配方.\\n&7[&#EBA844Kanthal Coils allow our &#816DF7Electric Blast Furnace to run at much higher &#F76D6Dtemperature, allowing more recipes to work.]&f"
		""
		"你必须在&#816DF7&a电力高炉&f&r的GUI中更换线圈.\\n&7[You must switch the coils in the GUI of &#816DF7Electric Blast Furnace.]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/modernindustrialization/switch_to_kanthal.png width:150 height:75 align:center}"
	]
	quest.39A0BA6E2A72A681.quest_desc: ["混合&#99F0F0不锈钢&r、&#ADDBDB铝&r和&#E9A8F7&a铬粉&f&r,将得到&#EBA844&a坎塔尔合金粉&f&r.\\n&7[Mixing &#99F0F0Stainless Steel, &#ADDBDBAluminium and &#E9A8F7Chromium Dust will give us &#EBA844Kanthal Dust.]&f"]
	quest.3A0C8BCE197A448B.quest_desc: ["&#827AFF丁苯橡胶&r可以与&#9683F7&a小撮铅粉&f&r或&#FEA8FF铬&a小撮粉末&f&r混合,得到&#A1A1A1&a丁苯橡胶&f&r.\\n&7[&#827AFFStyrene-Butadiene can be mixed with either  &#9683F7Lead Tiny Dust or &#FEA8FFChromium Tiny Dust to get &#A1A1A1Styrene-Butadiene Rubber.]&f"]
	quest.3ACC27B786CDCF22.quest_desc: ["一台&#3ABEC7&a电力压缩机&f允许你将&#CE5ADB&a小撮钨粉&f&r变成&#AF22BF&a钨粒&f&r.\\n&7[An &#3ABEC7Electric Compressor allows you to turn &#CE5ADBTungsten Tiny Dust into &#AF22BFTungsten Nuggets.]&f"]
	quest.3B1CDC2DD05CAE80.quest_desc: ["&#F36EF5聚&a氯乙烯&f&r与&#6EBAF5&a铂板&f、&#C4C362&a镉电池&f&r、&#F7BB57&a退火铜&f电缆&r和&#57BFF7&a数字电路板&f&r结合,将得到&#EBE56E&a处理单元板&f&r.\\n&7[&#F36EF5PolyVinyl Chloride with &#6EBAF5Platinum Plate, &#C4C362Cadmium Battery, &#F7BB57Annealed Copper Cable and &#57BFF7Digital Circuit Board will give us &#EBE56EProcessing Unit Board.]&f"]
	quest.3CB05026BC4C5577.quest_desc: ["目前,你可以非常低效地在&#6F93C7&a电力压缩机&f&r中使用&#3946E3混合抗爆合金锭&r来制作&#986FC7&a抗爆合金板&f&r.\\n&7[As of now, you can very inefficiently make &#986FC7Blastproof Alloy Plates in an &#6F93C7Electric Compressor using the &#3946E3Mixed Blastproof Ingot.]&f"]
	quest.3FE2A649F07DF28D.quest_subtitle: "你可以粉碎&d极限反应堆&f的蓝托尼姆来获得&a钚粉&f&7[You can crush Extreme Reactors Blutonium for Plutonium Dust]&f"
	quest.3FE489E6B1FAC24B.quest_subtitle: "回收耗竭燃料棒&7[Recycling the Depleted Rods]&f"
	quest.3FE489E6B1FAC24B.title: "获取钚&7[Getting Plutonium]&f"
	quest.40F2EDB9384CE782.quest_desc: ["蒸馏&#DBE37F蒸汽裂解&a轻燃油&f&r将得到&#9C6C35乙炔&r作为产物.\\n&7[Distilling &#DBE37FSteam Cracked Light Fuel will give you &#9C6C35Acetylene as a product.]&f"]
	quest.4A06CCE1FE0F333C.quest_desc: ["将&#74C3DB&a进气口&f&r放入&#46CAF2&a真空冷冻机&f&r中,你将获得&#B5E7F7&a液态空气&f&r.\\n&7[The &#74C3DBAir Intake when put in a &#46CAF2Vacuum Freezer will yield you &#B5E7F7Liquid Air.]&f"]
	quest.4A618CA66AD6223D.quest_subtitle: "更高的能量输入&7[Even more power input]&f"
	quest.4F870252E9FB1A41.quest_desc: ["反应堆可以由&a燃料棒&f供能,这些是你能制作的最基础的燃料棒.\\n&7[Reactor can be fueled by Fuel Rods, these are the most basic ones you can craft.]&f"]
	quest.50F97171D25CD2EE.quest_desc: ["&#6EDDFF涡轮升级&r每个升级增加&#FFEB6E512 EU/t&r的容量.\\n&7[&#6EDDFFTurbo Upgrades add &#FFEB6E512EU/t of capacity per upgrade.]&f"]
	quest.56A4F5D301BC1E93.quest_desc: ["&#6EDDFF涡轮升级&r每个升级增加&#FFEB6E64 EU/t&r的容量.\\n&7[&#6EDDFFTurbo Upgrades add &#FFEB6E64EU/t of capacity per upgrade.]&f"]
	quest.58F7C11C241DD7A4.quest_desc: [
		"&#6AADD9&a蒸馏塔&f&r是&#A3D2F0蒸馏器&r的升级版.它的主要优点是对同一输入提供多种输出.\\n&7[The &#6AADD9Distillation Tower is the upgraded form of &#A3D2F0Distillery. Its major benefit is that it gives you multiple outputs for the same input.]&f"
		""
		"To build the structure, you must open the GUI of the &#6AADD9Distillation Tower block and choose the height. Height depends on how many outputs you need. To process &#76759ECrude Oil, you need a height of 3 blocks."
	]
	quest.58F7C11C241DD7A4.quest_subtitle: "&a效率&f至关重要&7[Efficiency matters]&f"
	quest.5A4406F89DB802F0.quest_desc: ["&#BB95CF苯乙烯&r与&#D46C85丁二烯&r之间的反应生成&#827AFF丁苯橡胶&r.\\n&7[Reaction between &#BB95CFStyrene and &#D46C85Butadiene leads to &#827AFFStyrene-Butadiene.]&f"]
	quest.5B45AB96953FA61C.title: "数字时代&7[The Digital Age]&f"
	quest.633D6361DA680C75.quest_desc: ["将&#E6ED98&a轻燃油&f&r与蒸汽混合,你将得到&#DBE37F蒸汽裂解&a轻燃油&f&r.\\n&7[Mixing &#E6ED98Light Fuel with Steam will yield you &#DBE37FSteam Cracked Light Fuel.]&f"]
	quest.66E78F599CD50579.quest_desc: [
		"&#49C472&a核反应堆&f&r允许你处理更高端的资源.我们将用它来生成&#8F49C4氘&r和&#EB5266氚&r.\\n&7[The &#49C472Nuclear Reactor allows you to process for higher end resources. We will be using it to generate &#8F49C4Deuterium and &#EB5266Tritium.]&f"
		""
		"这份资源清单将帮助你建造一个”大型”反应堆.由于其速度和效率,不建议建造任何更小的尺寸.\\n&7[This resource list will help you build a \"Large\" Reactor. Any smaller size is not recommended due to its speed and efficiency.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"制造高效反应堆的细节过于复杂,无法在此提供.不过,我会在这里为你提供可能的最佳设计.\\n&7[The details of making an efficient reactor are far too complicated to be provided here. I will provide you with the best designs possible here though.]&f"
		""
		"这是一个用于生产&#8F49C4氘&r的&#49C472大型反应堆&r设计.\\n&7[Here is a &#49C472Large Reactor design to produce &#8F49C4Deuterium.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/modernindustrialization/large_reactor.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		""
		"这是用于生产&#EB5266氚&r的&#49C472极限尺寸反应堆&r设计.\\n&7[This is the &#49C472Extreme sized Reactor design to produce &#EB5266Tritium.]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/modernindustrialization/largest_reactor.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.66E78F599CD50579.quest_subtitle: "它们不会爆炸&7[They don't explode]&f"
	quest.672B69448F1D458B.quest_desc: ["&#FAAD28&a热交换器&f&r是&#4D7DFF&d极限反应堆&f&r涡轮爱好者的天堂.这台机器可以产生极其大量的蒸汽.\\n&7[The &#FAAD28Heat Exchanger is haven for the &#4D7DFFExtreme Reactors Turbine lovers. This machine can produce an extonishingly large amount of Steam.]&f"]
	quest.672B69448F1D458B.quest_subtitle: "蒸汽呼呼响&7[Steam go brrr]&f"
	quest.6A9AE3514B5151C9.quest_desc: ["&#CFB951坎塔尔线圈&r将允许我们将&#C356C4&a粗钛&f&r加工成&#DF9DE0&a热钛锭&f&r.这个过程需要&#D49B70&a硫化锰溶液&f&r.\\n&7[&#CFB951Kanthal Coils will allow us to process &#C356C4Raw Titanium into &#DF9DE0Titanium Hot Ingots. This process requires &#D49B70Manganese Sulfuric Solution.]&f"]
	quest.6F183B06683D1213.quest_desc: ["&#EBA844&a热坎塔尔合金锭&f&r可以使用&#6DC0F7&a真空冷冻机&f&r冷却.\\n&7[The &#EBA844Kanthal Hot Ingot can be cooled down using the &#6DC0F7Vacuum Freezer.]&f"]
	quest.6F3974CAAA555FD0.quest_subtitle: "管理这个RAM&7[Managing this RAM]&f"
	quest.75619C7174C6703C.quest_desc: ["离心&a铀粉&f将给我们一些铀的同位素,这些同位素可以进一步加工成更好的燃料棒.\\n&7[Centrifuging the Uranium Dust will give us some isotopes of Uranium which can be further processed into better rods.]&f"]
	quest.75619C7174C6703C.title: "离心&a铀粉&f&7[Centrifuging Uranium Dust]&f"
	quest.78EC7D19BE24FE06.quest_subtitle: "它不会爆炸&7[It does not explode]&f"
	quest.7AF6C95816E82861.quest_desc: ["&#5B75D4化学反应&r&#8F49C4氘&r与&#AABBFA氧气&r,将得到&#9C51DB&a重水&f&r.这可以放回&#45BF56反应堆&r中.\\n&7[&#5B75D4Chemically Reacting the &#8F49C4Deuterium with &#AABBFAOxygen will give us &#9C51DBHeavy Water. This can be put back into the &#45BF56Reactor.]&f"]
	quest.7C73740F1B515F2C.quest_desc: ["&#C452C4&a钨粉&f&r需要被分解成更小的变体,以便进行加工.\\n&7[&#C452C4Tungsten Dust needs to be broken down to a much smaller variant to allow its processing.]&f"]
	task.08F68CC089765088.title: "绕过技巧&7[Bypass Trick]&f"
	quest.068128395837AF4F.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽一体&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.08C870DC50CA49FC.quest_desc: [
		"&#5C5C5C&a原油&f&r本身对我们没有太大用处,但通过蒸馏器处理后,我们得到的输出可以用于许多许多用途.\\n&7[&#5C5C5CCrude Oil on its own is not of much use to us but when put through a distillery, we get outputs that can be used for many many purposes.]&f"
		""
		"我们可以用它生产&#C4C241&a含硫重燃油&f&r、&#CECC5F&a含硫轻燃油&f&r和&#D9D782含硫石脑油&r.\\n&7[We can produce &#C4C241Sulfuric Heavy Fuel, &#CECC5FSulfuric Light Fuel and &#D9D782Sulfuric Naptha with it.]&f"
	]
	quest.08C870DC50CA49FC.title: "&#5C5C5C原油&a处理&f&7[&#5C5C5CCrude Oil Processing]&f"
	quest.0903F0D8642449B7.quest_desc: ["从&6模拟电路&r过渡,我们现在可以处理超过2位的信息.这为一些新机器打开了视野.\\n&7[Moving from analog circuitry, we can now process more than 2 bits of information. This opens horizons for some new machines]&f"]
	quest.0A9ADDE68342B987.quest_desc: [
		"要制作&#43DEC2聚乙烯&r,你需要遵循以下化学链:\\n&7[To make &#43DEC2Polyethylene, you follow the chain of chemicals this way:]&f"
		""
		"&8原油&r -> &#D2CD2D&a含硫轻燃油&f&r -> &#DBD658&a轻燃油&f&r -> &#E2DF78蒸汽裂解轻燃油&r -> &#44D1DB乙烯&r -> &#43DEC2聚乙烯&r.\\n&7[Crude oil -> &#D2CD2DSulfuric Light Fuel-> &#DBD658Light Fuel-> &#E2DF78Steam Cracked Light fuel -> &#44D1DBEthylene -> &#43DEC2Polyethylene.]&f"
	]
	quest.0C94D76B87E49FFD.title: "铁处理&7[Iron Processing]&f"
	quest.103728F2BAD5AE84.title: "高级组件&7[Advanced Components]&f"
	quest.1351D0594F1E6551.quest_desc: ["这些&#55EDA4基础组件&r将引领我们进入加工领域的下一个突破.\\n&7[These &#55EDA4basic components will lead us into the next breakthrough in processing.]&f"]
	quest.1351D0594F1E6551.title: "电路组件&7[Circuit Components]&f"
	quest.162807D14C173CB4.quest_desc: ["&#5599ED离心机&r证实了我们的理论:如果我们把某物旋转得足够快,一种新材料就会从中掉出来.它有很多用途,但你主要需要它来处理&#F2AAE5铬&r和&#AD3497独居石&r.\\n&7[The &#5599EDCentrifuge confirmed our theory if we spin something fast enough a new material just plops out of it. It has a lot of uses but you will need it mainly for &#F2AAE5Chromium and &#AD3497Monazite processing. ]&f"]
	quest.162807D14C173CB4.quest_subtitle: "你让我的头转啊转啊转……&7[You spin my head right round right round..]&f"
	quest.1745124F83D033B9.title: "基础组件&7[Basic Components]&f"
	quest.18C0EF38430C3E67.quest_subtitle: "数字时代&7[The Digital Age]&f"
	quest.1A84DF4478D55C41.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽一体&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.1B4CD5AC8F6C3307.quest_desc: ["&#4497DB超频模块&r即使在当前没有运行配方时也能保持机器的效率.作为交换,它会将机器锁定为该配方.\\n&7[The &#4497DBOverdrive module preserves the efficiency of the machine even when the recipe is not currently running. In return it locks the machine for the recipe.]&f"]
	quest.1E0EF28175A7424F.quest_desc: ["既然你已经在生产蒸汽,何不利用它来发电呢.只需放置一个&#6363DB涡轮机&r,输入&7蒸汽&r,然后输出&#DBDB63电力&r.\\n&7[Since you are already producing the steam, why not use it to make electricity. Simply slap down a &#6363DBTurbine and put steam in and pull &#DBDB63electricity out.]&f"]
	quest.1E0EF28175A7424F.quest_subtitle: "蒸汽 -> 电力&7[Steam -> Electricity]&f"
	quest.1F21B578FAF4CCAC.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽一体&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.1F3E18129B871C49.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽一体&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.22AD9DF2BCC04575.quest_subtitle: "创造能量&7[Creating the energy]&f"
	quest.22AD9DF2BCC04575.title: "&a发电装置&f&7[Electricity Generation]&f"
	quest.256C3DBA392B4236.quest_desc: ["电解锰和铬的酸性溶液,将得到它们的粉末,可用于未来的配方.\\n&7[Electrolysing the Acidic Solutions for Manganese and Chromium will yield you their Dusts which can be used for future recipes.]&f"]
	quest.256C3DBA392B4236.quest_subtitle: "9个&a小撮粉末&f合成1个粉末&7[9 Tiny Dusts give 1 Dust]&f"
	quest.2EF0C033C540A7B1.title: "红宝石处理&7[Ruby Processing]&f"
	quest.32D585D9F73CD9FD.quest_desc: ["&#EDDF55&a电力高炉&f&r将允许你熔炼几种不同的资源.配方需要使用结构中的&#B8ED55特定线圈&r.\\n&7[The &#EDDF55Electric Blast Furnace will allow you to cook several different resources. The recipes do require a &#B8ED55specific coil to be used in the structure.]&f"]
	quest.374C06B3999BB0D3.quest_desc: ["混合&#C2C78B铁&r、&#EDB2EA铬&r、&#BEC9A3镍&r和&7锰&r,你将得到&#ADF0EE不锈钢&a钢粉&f&r.\\n&7[Mixing together &#C2C78BIron, &#EDB2EAChromium, &#BEC9A3Nickel and Manganese will give you &#ADF0EEStainless Steel Dust.]&f"]
	quest.3A03852E282DAA4D.quest_desc: ["&#ED8055电解机&r能够提供足够的突发能量给材料,使它们分解成更基础的资源.\\n&7[The &#ED8055Electrolyzer is able to provide enough energy in bursts to material that they break down to more fundamental resources.]&f"]
	quest.3B9D9CB589DB2003.quest_desc: [
		"&#71EBB4&n&d现代工业化&f&r的机器与其他模组的工作方式不同.所有机器都有一个&#E5EB71效率倍率&r,当机器运行它制造的配方时,这个倍率会上升.&#E5EB71效率&r提高机器的&#E5EB71速度&r.当配方改变时,&#E5EB71效率&r会重置.\\n&7[&#71EBB4Modern Industrialization machines work differently to other mods. All machines have an &#E5EB71efficiency multiplier, this goes up as you have a recipe in the machine that it makes. &#E5EB71Efficiency increases the &#E5EB71speed of the machine. &#E5EB71Efficiency resets when recipe changes.]&f"
		""
		"建议你使用1台机器被动生产1种配方的组件.这就是这个模组预期的玩法.升级将使系统变得更好.这将在未来介绍.\\n&7[You are advised to use 1 machine for 1 recipe producing components passively. This is how the mod is supposed to be played. Upgrades will make the system better. This will be covered in the future.]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/modernindustrialization/prod_line.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"这个模组的所有机器都接受FE作为能源.&c16 FE&r转换为&#E1EB591 EU&r的电力.\\n&7[All machines from this mod accept FE as power. 16 FE converts to &#E1EB591 EU of power.]&f"
	]
	quest.3B9D9CB589DB2003.quest_subtitle: "这会有所帮助&7[This will help]&f"
	quest.3CE72DAF431269CD.quest_desc: ["&#D6AC2F极化器&r能够磁化放入其中的材料.\\n&7[The &#D6AC2FPolarizer is able to magnetise the materials put into it.]&f"]
	quest.401A3FD6A3511870.quest_subtitle: "芝麻开门&7[Open Sesame]&f"
	quest.401A3FD6A3511870.title: "门&7[Gates]&f"
	quest.401B559649C54C5C.quest_desc: ["混合&#92CCF0氢气&r和&#519BC9氯气&r,你将得到&#4FB373&a盐酸&f&r.这将用于处理&#F2A0E1&a铬粉&f&r.\\n&7[Mixing together &#92CCF0Hydrogen and &#519BC9Chlorine will give you &#4FB373Hydrochloric Acid. This will be used to process &#F2A0E1Chromium Dust.]&f"]
	quest.408EBED932656006.quest_desc: ["掺杂&7硅&r会比使用基础&7硅&r获得更好的产量.\\n&7[Doping Silicon will get you much better yield than using base Silicon.]&f"]
	quest.408EBED932656006.title: "掺杂硅&7[Doped Silicone]&f"
	quest.413F338DB07BA88C.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽的那个相同&7[Same as steam one]&f"
	quest.4A5A143A79809BB6.quest_desc: [
		"啊,是的,你终于做到了.欢迎来到电力时代,这是你冒险的真正开始.\\n&7[Ah yes, you finally made it. Welcome to the Electric Age, this is the real beginning of your adventure.]&f"
		""
		"首先,我们需要&a电池合金&f……来制造电池,我知道,这很令人震惊.\\n&7[First of all, we need Battery Alloy... to make batteries, shocking, I know.]&f"
	]
	quest.4A5A143A79809BB6.quest_subtitle: "&a电池合金&f&7[Battery Alloy]&f"
	quest.4A5A143A79809BB6.title: "&a电力&f时代&7[The Electric Age]&f"
	quest.4E7B1B16C7CDA84C.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽的那个相同&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.532BCAB3FBF91B1D.quest_desc: [
		"&#44DB9C升级&r为机器增加了进入&#4467DB超频&r状态的能力,进一步提高了机器的最大速度.\\n&7[&#44DB9CUpgrades add the ability for machines to move into &#4467DBoverclocked state further increasing the maximum speed of the machine.]&f"
		""
		"一台机器最多可以容纳任意等级的升级各一组.&#CEDB44基础升级&r每个升级增加&#F7F448+2 EU/t&r的容量.\\n&7[A machine can expect upto a stack of any tier of upgrades. The &#CEDB44Basic Upgrade adds &#F7F448+2EU/t to the capacity per upgrade.]&f"
	]
	quest.548274CC00E67EC4.quest_desc: ["传输电力很简单,你只需要在&#F5B027发电机&r和&#3CC1FA机器&r之间放一根电缆.低压电缆最多可以传输&#EEFA3C256 EU/t&r.\\n&7[Transferring electricity is simple, you just slap a cable in between your &#F5B027Generators and &#3CC1FAMachines. LV cables can transfer &#EEFA3C256 EU/t at most.]&f"]
	quest.548274CC00E67EC4.quest_subtitle: "电缆限制&7[Cable Limits]&f"
	quest.548274CC00E67EC4.title: "低压电缆&7[LV Cables]&f"
	quest.54CE9493B63620C4.quest_desc: ["&#AC59EB&a柴油发电机&f&r将各种液体燃料转化为电力.你早期最容易获得的是&7&a杂酚油&f&r和&8合成油&r.\\n&7[The &#AC59EBDiesel Generator converts a variety of liquid fuels to electricity. The most accessible for you early on will be Creosote Oil and Synthetic Oil.]&f"]
	quest.54CE9493B63620C4.quest_subtitle: "液体燃料 -> 电力&7[Liquid Fuels -> Electricity]&f"
	quest.55BB4005BB4CA316.title: "独居石处理&7[Monazite Processing]&f"
	quest.5A62260FB3850092.quest_desc: ["将&e硫&r、&#6ACDE6氧&r和&9水&r混合会得到&#D3D955&a硫酸&f&r.这将用于处理&7&a锰粉&f&r.\\n&7[Mixing together Sulfur, &#6ACDE6Oxygen and Water will give you &#D3D955Sulfuric Acid. This will be used to process Manganese Dust.]&f"]
	quest.5AA8D2A1F3618615.quest_subtitle: "传输电力&7[Moving electricity]&f"
	quest.5B50AC47957F0CD7.quest_desc: ["&7石油钻机&r将为你钻取&#7A7A7A&a页岩油&f&r和&#918686&a原油&f&r.\\n&7[The Oil Rig will drill up &#7A7A7AShale Oil and &#918686Crude Oil for you.]&f"]
	quest.5B50AC47957F0CD7.quest_subtitle: "鹰的叫声&7[Eagle noises]&f"
	quest.5D404ED40C6C2690.quest_subtitle: "输入更多能量&7[Input more power]&f"
	quest.604C003EE6B1CC6B.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽相同&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.6256612D46C88C0C.quest_desc: [
		"&#723CFA变压器&r将一种电压范围转换为另一种.\\n&7[&#723CFATransformers convert one range of power to another. ]&f"
		""
		"&#EBC471低压&r转&#DDE548中压&r &#723CFA变压器&r:将&#EBC471低压&r电力转换为&#DDE548中压&r电力,它有5个输入和1个输出.\\n&7[&#EBC471LV to &#DDE548MV &#723CFATransformers: Converts &#EBC471LV power to &#DDE548MV power, it has 5 inputs and 1 output.]&f"
		""
		"&#DDE548中压&r转&#EBC471低压&r &#723CFA变压器&r:将&#DDE548中压&r电力转换为&#EBC471低压&r电力,它有1个输入和5个输出.\\n&7[&#DDE548MV to &#EBC471LV &#723CFATransformers: Converts &#DDE548MV power to &#EBC471LV power, it has 1 input and 5 outputs.]&f"
	]
	quest.6256612D46C88C0C.quest_subtitle: "”自由是所有感知生命的权利”&7[\"Freedom is the right of all sentient beings\"]&f"
	quest.6256612D46C88C0C.title: "LV-&a中压变压器&f&7[LV-MV Transformers]&f"
	quest.6647A9652EFDDCDF.quest_desc: ["要冷却&#ADF0EE热不锈钢&a钢锭&f&r,只需将其放入&#56E3DF&a真空冷冻机&f&r中,即可将其转化为可用的&#ADF0EE不锈钢&a钢锭&f&r.\\n&7[To cool down the &#ADF0EEHot Stainless Steel Ingot simply put it into a &#56E3DFVacuum Freezer to turn it into usable &#ADF0EEStainless Steel Ingot.]&f"]
	quest.66D4256F79D5B30B.quest_subtitle: "与蒸汽相同&7[Same as steam as one]&f"
	quest.6A25ED4059E224D2.quest_desc: [
		"&#ED5585蒸馏室&r用于蒸馏某些流体,以获得更适合我们使用的、更好的产出物.\\n&7[The &#ED5585Distillery is used to distill certain fluids to receive better more fitting outputs for our use. ]&f"
		""
		"如果单一输入会产生多种输出,你必须锁定配方才能得到你想要的东西.首先点击GUI中的锁定图标,点击箭头,然后在你想要的配方上点击&7'+'&r图标.\\n&7[You must lock the recipe in order to get what you want if a singular input produces many outputs. First click on the lock icon in the GUI, click on the arrow and then '+' icon on your desired recipe. ]&f"
	]
	quest.6A25ED4059E224D2.quest_subtitle: "锁定配方&7[Lock the recipe]&f"
	quest.6E7DF4AF86A036EC.title: "页岩&a原油处理&f&7[Shale Oil Processing]&f"
	quest.72FFD9E471242D68.quest_desc: ["不锈钢需要比普通熔炉更高的热量来熔炼.我们必须使用之前建造的&a电力高炉&f.\\n&7[Stainless Steel requires more heat to smelt than a normal furnace. We must use our previously constructed Electric Blast Furnace.]&f"]
	quest.744E620B7DEBB483.quest_desc: ["&#27CFF5&a真空冷冻机&f&r将用于冷却&#E6AD1E热锭&r或某些流体,以获得你已经生产的物品的更好比例.\\n&7[The &#27CFF5Vacuum Freezer will be used to cooldown &#E6AD1EHot Ingots or certain fluids for better ratios of items you have already been producing.]&f"]
	quest.744E620B7DEBB483.quest_subtitle: "冰之凛冽&7[Bing Chilling]&f"
	quest.76660075F254597E.quest_desc: ["&#F5B758高级升级&r每个升级增加&#EDE02F16 EU/t&r的最大使用量.\\n&7[&#F5B758Advanced Upgrade adds &#EDE02F16 EU/t of maximum usage per upgrade.]&f"]
	quest.7E3B19796870C2B1.quest_desc: ["&#9955ED&a化学反应器&f&r将是你未来最有用的机器之一.它将用于制造多种化学品.\\n&7[The &#9955EDChemical Reactor will be one of the most useful machines for you going forward. It will be used to create several chemicals.]&f"]
	quest.7EDBE88A2CFAB353.quest_desc: [
		"&#562FD6装配机&r用于制造大量组件和机器.它们能够以自动化的方式进行合成工作.\\n&7[The &#562FD6Assemblers are used to make a lot of components and machines. They are able to do crafting jobs in an automatic manner.]&f"
		"它们还为你已经使用过的一些配方提供了&a便宜得多&r的变体.\\n&7[They also offer much cheaper variants of some recipes you have already used.]&f"
	]
	quest.7EDBE88A2CFAB353.quest_subtitle: "你会需要很多&7[You'll need many]&f"
	quest.7FE5864E59D7B827.quest_desc: ["&#6784EB外壳&r控制可以输入机器的能量上限.当你向机器放入升级时,你将需要更高等级的&#6784EB外壳&r来接受更多能量.&#6784EB外壳&r的等级也影响何种电缆可以连接到它.\\n&7[&#6784EBHulls control the amount of power that can be pushed into a machine. As you put upgrades into the machine, you will need a higher tier &#6784EBHull in it to accept more power. The tier of the &#6784EBHull also affects what cable can connect to it.]&f"]
	quest.7FE5864E59D7B827.quest_subtitle: "基础构建方块&7[Basic building block]&f"
	task.12433760FD40CB3A.title: "仔细阅读&7[Read this carefully]&f"
	task.1489DD401D237541.title: "电力&7[Electricity]&f"
	task.1FE598387B609AE5.title: "电力传输&7[Electricity Transfer]&f"
	quest.0AE83A6CC21F96D4.quest_desc: ["电解一个&#3127F5奇点&r将产生&#DA27F5&aUU物质&f&r.在此过程中,&#3127F5奇点&r&n&a不会被&r消耗.\\n&7[Electrolysing a &#3127F5Singularity will make &#DA27F5UU Matter. In this process, the &#3127F5Singularity is NOT consumed.]&f"]
	quest.1E22A0D5F4B2EB0D.quest_subtitle: "用氦气冷冻氩气&7[Freezing Argon with Helium]&f"
	quest.27826D74ADC73556.quest_desc: ["在&#E3CE54坎塔尔电力高炉&r中用&#90F0E7氧气&r烧制&#ED8C61&a铜粉&f&r,你将得到&#E87848&a热退火铜锭&f&r.这可以在&#4CBBD9&a真空冷冻机&f&r中冷却以获得&#E87848&a退火铜锭&f&r.这些锭可以被粉碎成&#E87848&a退火铜粉&f&r.\\n&7[Cooking &#ED8C61Copper Dust with &#90F0E7Oxygen in a &#E3CE54Kanthal EBF will give you &#E87848Annealed Copper Hot Ingot. This can be cooled down in a &#4CBBD9Vacuum Freezer to get &#E87848Annealed Copper Ingot. These ingots can be macerated for the &#E87848Annealed Copper Dust.]&f"]
	quest.3AB0822F02350DA3.quest_subtitle: "无限&a伤害&f&7[Infinite Damage]&f"
	quest.3B99290BE63F2968.quest_subtitle: "压缩&a碳粉&f&7[Compressing Carbon Dust]&f"
	quest.4F780343E3FFA43E.quest_subtitle: "&a结束了&f&7[This is the End]&f"
	quest.53C167AF34694F8F.quest_desc: ["将&#40B36A钇&r、&#DBA146&a退火铜&f&r、&#33CC3A钕&r和&#D6D290铱&r粉混合,将制成&#5EDEE0超导粉&r.这可以在&#E3CE54坎塔尔电力高炉&r中烧制,然后在&#4CBBD9&a真空冷冻机&f&r中冷却.\\n&7[Mixing together &#40B36AYttrium, &#DBA146Annealed Copper, &#33CC3ANeodymium and &#D6D290Iridium Dusts will make &#5EDEE0SuperConductor Dust. This can be cooked in a &#E3CE54Kanthal EBF to be cooled down in the &#4CBBD9Vacuum Freezer.]&f"]
	quest.53C167AF34694F8F.quest_subtitle: "超导&7[Conducting superly]&f"
	quest.54C852CA6E056589.quest_subtitle: "核电池&7[Nuclear Batteries]&f"
	quest.732DA855AFF62907.quest_desc: ["离心&8煤炭&r将制成&7&a碳粉&f&r.\\n&7[Centrifuging Coal will make Carbon Dust.]&f"]
	task.121A74E938A0320C.title: "&aUU物质&f&7[UU Matter]&f"
	quest.088CA7B6D4899846.quest_desc: ["&#65C2A6打包机&r用于制造&#53E67B双锭&r、&#53E67B刀片&r和&#53E67B电缆&r.除此之外,这台机器还有许多其他用途,但这些将是你主要用到的.\\n&7[The &#65C2A6Packer is used to create &#53E67BDouble Ingots, &#53E67BBlades and &#53E67BCables. Along with this there are many other uses for the machine but these will be the main ones for you.]&f"]
	quest.0DAF5D42694EA8C9.quest_desc: [
		"&#6E6D6D&n&a锻造锤子&f&r是你旅程的开始.它有很多用途,比如从你的矿石中获得&#B53A3A更好的产出&r,到为未来的合成制作&#DBD25A组件&r.\\n&7[&#6E6D6DForge Hammer is the beginning of your journey. It has a lot of uses like getting a &#B53A3Abetter output out of your ores to making &#DBD25Acomponents for future crafts.]&f"
		""
		"你合成的&7锤子&r不是配方所必需的,但它会为你制作的&#DBD25A组件&r提供更好的产出.\\n&7[The Hammer you crafted is not required for a recipe but it will give you a better output on the &#DBD25Acomponents you craft.]&f"
	]
	quest.0DAF5D42694EA8C9.title: "&#949494&a锻造锤子&f&7[&#949494Forge Hammer]&f"
	quest.1036837C9AD3F301.quest_desc: ["&#6E6D6D&a锻造锤子&f&r将使你能够轻松地将&#FFAC3B铜&r锭或矿石形态粉碎成其粉末.\\n&7[The &#6E6D6DForge Hammer will allow you to easily crush &#FFAC3BCopper Ingots or Ore forms into its Dusts.]&f"]
	quest.12F9705ACB8FB300.quest_desc: [
		"&#EDD653&n&a金属剪切机&f&r使你能够进行许多合成.重要的是螺栓.\\n&7[The &#EDD653Cutting Machine enables you to do a lot of crafts. The important ones are the Bolts. ]&f"
		""
		"&#EDD653&n剪切机&r需要使用&#E3993D润滑剂&r工作,润滑剂通过使用&#EDD653&n搅拌机&r获得.\\n&7[&#EDD653Cutting machine works with &#E3993DLubricant which is obtained by using the &#EDD653Mixer.]&f"
	]
	quest.12FB3990CA1653A4.quest_desc: [
		"&#DBA15A蒸汽钻机&r将是你早期挖矿的最佳伙伴.它能够进行&5 3x3&r的挖掘区域,并且具有&#EEF768可切换的精准采集&r.\\n&7[The &#DBA15ASteam Drill will be your best friend for early game mining. It is able to do a 3 by 3 mining area as well as have a &#EEF768toggle-able silk touch.]&f"
		""
		"你可以通过按下按键绑定”切换&a3x3挖掘&f”来切换&5 3x3&r挖掘,默认设置为&7'Y'&r.\\n&7[You can toggle 3 by 3 mining by pressing the keybind \"Toggle 3x3 Mining\" which is default set to 'Y'.]&f"
		""
		"&#EEF768&a精准采集&f&r可以通过&7潜行右击&r蒸汽钻机来切换\\n&7[&#EEF768Silk Touch can be toggled by Sneak Right-Clicking the Steam Drill]&f"
		""
		"要给&#DBA15A蒸汽钻机&r填充燃料,你可以将钻机悬停在物品栏中的&6燃料&r上并&7右击&r.&9水&r可以在世界中&7右击&r,或者你可以随身携带一桶水.\\n&7[To fill the &#DBA15ASteam Drill, you can hold the drill over a fuel in your inventory and Right-Click. Water can be either Right-Clicked in world or you can carry a water bucket around.]&f"
	]
	quest.1C9D3FC67D58AC02.quest_desc: ["&#EDD653&n搅拌机&r将使我们能够组合物品和流体.它们可用于给物品染色,甚至复制它们.\\n&7[The &#EDD653Mixer will allow us to combine items and fluids. They can be used to dye items or even duplicate them.]&f"]
	quest.1E4E462928F2A71C.quest_desc: [
		"&7&n&a焦炉&f&r将用于将&#787777煤炭&r转化为&#696464焦炭&r.&#696464焦炭&r作为燃料的效果是&#787777煤炭&r的&a 4 倍&f.\\n&7[The Coke Oven will be used to convert &#787777Coal to &#696464Coke. &#696464Coke is 4 times as effective as a fuel than &#787777Coal. ]&f"
		""
		"多方块结构可以通过在你的副手或主手中持有&#D1D15E扳手&r来预览.手中持有&#B4D95D仓口&r会告诉你它们可能的位置.\\n&7[The multiblock can be previewed by holding a &#D1D15Ewrench in your off or main hand. Holding &#B4D95Dhatches in your hand will tell you the possible positions for them.]&f"
		""
		"&7&n&a焦炉&f&r是一个主要由砖块构成的中空多方块结构.\\n&7[The Coke Oven is a hollow multiblock made up of mostly bricks.]&f"
	]
	quest.21A4FE1741E4E78C.quest_desc: [
		"&#65C2A6采石场&r是一个用于生成资源的多方块结构.它需要&a钻头&r和&7蒸汽&r才能运作.\\n&7[The &#65C2A6Quarry is a multiblock to generate resources. It requires Drills and Steam to function.]&f"
		""
		"每次运行都有消耗&a钻头&r的几率.更好的&a钻头&r提供更好的资源.\\n&7[Every iteration has a chance of consuming the Drill. Better Drills give better resources.]&f"
		""
		"&a开采机&f只能使用&#DEA14B铜&r和&#DE9531&a青铜钻&f&r.它也可以使用&#8A5C1E泥土&r来生成石头.\\n&7[Steam Quarry can only use &#DEA14BCopper and &#DE9531Bronze Drills. It can also use &#8A5C1EDirt to generate Stones.]&f"
	]
	quest.21A4FE1741E4E78C.quest_subtitle: "无限资源&7[Infinite Resources]&f"
	quest.23708582B1064C9D.quest_desc: ["一个&#46DBBB电路&r将需要一些这些基础组件才能工作,自动化这些部分在未来将很有用.\\n&7[A &#46DBBBCircuit will require some of these basic components to function, automating parts of these will be useful in the future.]&f"]
	quest.23708582B1064C9D.title: "电容与电阻&7[Capacitance and Resistance]&f"
	quest.24285F25F9563B02.quest_desc: ["&#467FDB&n&a模拟电路&f&r,啊!你终于做出来了.通常其他人花的时间只有你的一半,但我不会因此责怪你……\\n&7[The &#467FDBAnalog Circuit, ah! you finally made it. Usually other people took half as much time as you but I won't hold this against you...]&f"]
	quest.24285F25F9563B02.quest_subtitle: "电子学基础&7[Basics of Electronics]&f"
	quest.253822C64BBBB1EB.quest_desc: ["&#6E6D6D&a锻造锤子&f&r将使你能够轻松地将&#9AD5ED锡&r锭或矿石形态粉碎成其粉末.\\n&7[The &#6E6D6DForge Hammer will allow you to easily crush &#9AD5EDTin Ingots or Ore forms into its Dusts.]&f"]
	quest.357DDE894EB512F7.quest_desc: ["&#65C2A6线材轧机&r能够施加恰到好处的力来为我们制造&#53E67B线材&r.震惊!!我知道……\\n&7[The &#65C2A6Wiremill is able to apply just the right amount of force to make &#53E67BWires for us. Shocking!! I know...]&f"]
	quest.3AA4D1B60E4E71A5.quest_desc: ["所有&c多方块结构&r都由放入其中的&e仓口&r定义.在&c多方块结构&r中升级这些&e仓口&r将整体升级机器.\\n&7[All multiblocks are defined by the hatches put in them. Upgrading these hatches in the multiblocks will upgrade the machine as a whole.]&f"]
	quest.41877F44CD3D1EDB.quest_desc: ["&#E3BC19&a青铜熔炉&f&r的作用就像普通熔炉一样,主要区别在于它使用蒸汽运行,并且速度快两倍.\\n&7[The &#E3BC19Bronze Furnace acts just like a regular one, only major difference is it runs on steam and is twice as fast.]&f"]
	quest.458BFDB636F8B495.quest_desc: ["将焦炭粉与铁结合将得到&a生钢粉&f.在&a蒸汽高炉&f中烧制它将产出你未来进展所需的&a钢锭&f.\\n&7[Combining the Coke dust with Iron will give Uncooked Steel Dust. Cooking it in the Steam Blast Furnace will yield you Steel Ingots required for future progression.]&f"]
	quest.478C1AF86610A8B7.quest_desc: ["&#EDD653&n压缩机&r用于制造&#53EDAA板&r、&#53EDAA弯曲板&r和&#53EDAA环&r.\\n&7[The &#EDD653Compressor is used to make &#53EDAAPlates, &#53EDAACurved Plates and &#53EDAARings.]&f"]
	quest.48F77A0BE1F33B29.quest_desc: ["使用新建造的&#65C2A6线材轧机&r,我们现在可以制造&#53E67B线材&r和&#53E67B细线&r,这将引领我们进入电气领域.\\n&7[Using the newly constructed &#65C2A6Wiremill, we can now make &#53E67BWires and &#53E67BFine Wires which will lead us into electrics.]&f"]
	quest.48F77A0BE1F33B29.title: "可怕的线&7[Dire Wire]&f"
	quest.4E69C6ABFE467C25.quest_desc: ["&#65C2A6&a合金炉&f&r来自&#3187C4扩展工业化&r.它将&#4C4BDE搅拌机&r和&#954BDE熔炉&r的任务合二为一,从而使工作不那么繁琐.\\n&7[The &#65C2A6Alloy Smelter comes from &#3187C4Extended Industrialization. It combines the task of &#4C4BDEMixer and &#954BDEFurnace into one, hence making the job less tedious.]&f"]
	quest.55C6BBC996B51838.quest_desc: [
		"&#ED9553&a青铜锅炉&f&r将&9水&r转化为蒸汽.蒸汽将作为你的机器在&7&n蒸汽时代&r工作的燃料.\\n&7[&#ED9553Bronze Boiler converts water into steam. Steam will act as fuel for your machines to work in the Steam Age.]&f"
		""
		"要使用这台机器,只需为其提供&9水&r和任何&#ED5353熔炉燃料&r.这将提高机器的温度,在最高温度下,它将能够同时处理4台机器.\\n&7[To use the machine, simply provide it with water and any &#ED5353furnace fuel. This will raise the temperature of the machine, at maximum temperature it will be able to handle 4 machines simultaneously.]&f"
	]
	quest.55C6BBC996B51838.quest_subtitle: "烧水&7[Boiling water]&f"
	quest.589DFDB8FB7211AA.quest_desc: ["为你进入&#C1DB46&n&a电力&f时代&r生产&7橡胶&r是轻而易举的.尽早自动化它将带你走得更远,超乎你的想象.\\n&7[Production of Rubber for your move into &#C1DB46The Electric Age is trivial. Automating it at the earliest will take you further than you believe.]&f"]
	quest.589DFDB8FB7211AA.title: "橡胶和&a电路板&f&7[Rubber and Circuit Board]&f"
	quest.5CCF92238B23EDC9.quest_desc: [
		"&#A0DE45&n&d现代工业化&f&r是一个模组,其性质类似于&#D93D3DIC2&r和&#D93D3D&d格雷科技&f&r,但你必须以不同于这两个模组的方式进展.\\n&7[&#A0DE45Modern Industrialization is a mod which is similar to &#D93D3DIC2 and &#D93D3DGregTech in its nature but you must progress differently than those 2 mods.]&f"
		""
		"通过这些任务,我将指导你制作&#43E898无限护甲&r所需的部件.\\n&7[Through these quests, I will guide you to making parts required for the &#43E898Infinity Armor.]&f"
	]
	quest.5CCF92238B23EDC9.quest_subtitle: "阅读会有帮助&7[Reading will help]&f"
	quest.5CCF92238B23EDC9.title: "&#A0DE45欢迎来到&d现代工业化&f&7[&#A0DE45Welcome to Modern Industrialization]&f"
	quest.5E191081662C2F1A.quest_desc: ["&#6E6D6D&a锻造锤子&f&r充当&#A0DE45&d现代工业化&f&r村民的工作站方块.这个村民将为你提供各种有用的交易.\\n&7[The &#6E6D6DForge Hammer acts as the workstation block for the &#A0DE45Modern Industrialization villager. This villager will give you a wide variety of useful trades.]&f"]
	quest.68EAB0248989FC97.quest_desc: [
		"&#EDD653&n&a蒸汽高炉&f&r开启了新的进展视野.这将是你在未来事业中的一个关键多方块结构.\\n&7[The &#EDD653Steam Blast Furnace unlocks new horizons of progression. This will be a key multiblock in your future endeavours.]&f"
		""
		"这个多方块结构不仅能让你制造&7&a钢锭&f&r,还能将&#696E60粗合成油&r加工成&#494D43合成油&r,后者将用于&#36472A橡胶&r和更多东西.\\n&7[Not only will this multiblock allow you to make Steel Ingots but also it allows processing of &#696E60Raw Synthetic Oil to &#494D43Synthetic Oil which will be used later for &#36472ARubber and more things.]&f"
	]
	quest.7282DCB1547CEB63.quest_desc: ["&#ED9553青铜&r将成为&7&n蒸汽时代&r的基石.烧制这种粉末将得到我们进一步使用的&#ED9553&a青铜锭&f&r.\\n&7[&#ED9553Bronze will act as the building block of the Steam Age. Cooking this dust will get you the &#ED9553Bronze Ingots we'll further use.]&f"]
	quest.7282DCB1547CEB63.title: "&#EDD653青铜&7[&#EDD653Bronze]&f"
	quest.7A873E48E38B5C0E.quest_desc: ["钢制机器使用的蒸汽量是青铜机器的两倍,但它们也以两倍的速度提升来弥补.\\n&7[Steel Machines use twice as much steam as the Bronze ones but they also make up for it with the twice the speed increase.]&f"]
	quest.7D220876E8FF7AED.quest_desc: [
		"&#65C2A6解包器&r有很多用途,从能够将&#53E67B方块解包成锭&r等等,到&#53E67B回收机器部件&r.\\n&7[The &#65C2A6Unpacker has a lot of uses from being able to unpack &#53E67BBlock into Ingots and more to &#53E67Brecycling parts of machines.]&f"
		""
		"&o你甚至可以从它那里更容易地获得&a硅锭&f.&r\\n&7[You can even get easier Silicon Ingots from it.]&f"
	]
	task.198A217D6A4C951C.title: "&a村民交易&f&7[Villager Trades]&f"
	task.31BE41B971794377.title: "钢铁时代&7[Steel Age]&f"
	task.45C5CAC94406DF41.title: "多方块等级&7[Multiblock Levels]&f"
	quest.00E1F1279F97557B.quest_desc: ["类似于挤压机MK1,但这个更先进!&a可用于&f图案,所以当方块被放置时,它们会按照那个图案排列!\\n&7[Similar to the Extruder MK1 but this one is more evolved! Can be used with Patterns so when Blocks are placed they will go in that pattern!]&f"]
	quest.01C5D8357D8B0D62.quest_desc: ["如果你知道&a探测轨道&f的工作原理,那么这个模块对你来说就很容易理解了.\\n\\n基本上,如果路由器中有某个物品,它会从路由器发出一个&a红石信号&f.\\n\\n在模块中,你可以设置物品、信号来源以及信号强度.\\n&7[If you know how a Detector Rail works then this Module will be explanatory for you. \\n\\nBasically if a certain Item is in the Router, it will emit a Redstone Signal out of the Router. \\n\\nIn the Module you can set the Item, where the Signal comes from, and how strong a Signal.]&f"]
	quest.067AB3E4C4492F0D.quest_desc: [
		"不想自己挖一大堆矿石？何不让路由器代劳？\\n\\n你可以使用放置器放下矿石,然后让附魔破坏器开采它们.破坏器需要先用制作它的镐进行附魔,模块本身无法附魔.\\n\\n你可能需要另一个路由器来拾取掉落的矿石.\\n&7[Don't feel like Mining a bunch of Ores you got? Why not let Routers do it for you? \\n\\nYou can use a Placer to place down the Ores, then let an Enchanted Breaker Mine the Ores. Breaker needs the Pickaxe used to craft it to be Enchanted first, the Module itself can't be Enchanted. \\n\\nYou might need another Router to pick up the dropped Ores.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/router/router_break.png width:150 height:80 align:center}"
	]
	quest.067AB3E4C4492F0D.title: "用于采矿的路由器&7[Routers for Mining]&f"
	quest.09E25B1CD6CABD5A.quest_desc: ["这个升级使路由器类似于一个框架方块.\\n\\n潜行并&a右击&f一个方块以将路由器的外观变为该方块.\\n\\n只是别把它弄丢了!\\n&7[This upgrade makes the Router similar to a Framed Block. \\n\\nSneak Right Click a Block to change the Routers appearance to it. \\n\\nJust don't lose it!]&f"]
	quest.0CE236731DF15DFF.quest_desc: ["为何要等待？通常Minecraft中掉落的物品需要一秒钟才能落地并被再次拾取.\\n\\n但何必等待呢？\\n\\n这个升级让&a真空模块&f无需等待,立即拾取物品.\\n\\n对减少卡顿非常有用!\\n&7[Why wait? Usually items dropped in Minecraft have a second they need to hit the ground to be picked up again. \\n\\nBut why wait?\\n\\nThis upgrade lets the Vacuum Module not wait and immediately pick up the items. \\n\\nVery good for less lag!]&f"]
	quest.0D5691403AEC25A8.quest_desc: [
		"路由器也可用于农业!\\n\\n首先从一个简单的农场开始.然后你需要一个&a执行模块&f并将其指向作物.之后,在你的路由器中放入一个&a真空模块&f来收集作物.最后将所有东西放入路由器,用红石供能,让它自动耕种!\\n&7[Routers can also be used for Farming!\\n\\nFirst start off with a simple Farm. Then you'll need an Activator Module and direct it toward the Crops. After that, put a Vacuum Module in your Router to collect the Crops. Finally put it all in the Router, Power it with Redstone, and let it farm!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/router/router_farm.png width:60 height:150 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0D5691403AEC25A8.title: "用于农业的路由器&7[Routers for Farming]&f"
	quest.0DC8B68CDF945348.quest_desc: ["&a路由器&f给予,路由器也索取.\\n\\n这个模块对建筑者甚至矿工都很有帮助!它可以设置为将其缓存中的物品发送到你的物品栏,或者从你的物品栏中取出物品放入其缓存.\\n\\n非常适合露天采矿,让它从你的物品栏中拿走所有圆石和深板岩,然后放进一个&a垃圾桶&f.\\n&7[The Router giveth and the Router taketh. \\n\\nThis Module is helpful for Builders or even Miners! It can be set to send items from its Buffer to your Inventory or take items from your Inventory into its Buffer. \\n\\nPerfect for Strip-Mining, have it take all the Cobble and Deepslate from your Inventory and put it in a Trash Can.]&f"]
	quest.10672B5991E5FC34.quest_desc: ["这是我的东西,别碰.\\n\\n放入此升级后,只有你能使用和操作这个路由器.\\n&7[It's my stuff, no touchy. \\n\\nOnly you can use and mess with the Router after putting in the Upgrade.]&f"]
	quest.1069244EB72F64CA.quest_desc: ["使用&a能量模块&f会消耗更多能量!\\n&7[Takes more Energy with the Energy Modules!]&f"]
	quest.143AE6889BDA9EF5.quest_desc: ["模块的过滤物品槽位有限,如果你需要更多,就用这个!批量物品过滤器.\\n\\n你可以放入更多物品来设置&a白名单或黑名单&f.然后把它扔到普通过滤器该放的地方!\\n\\n制作更多独特过滤器时会需要它!\\n&7[Modules only have so many slots for Filtered Items, if you need more than use this! Bulk Item Filter. \\n\\nYou can put many more Items in to Whitelist or Blacklist in it. Then throw it in where normal Filters go! \\n\\nWill be needed to craft more unique Filters!]&f"]
	quest.177396B9C4F9B3E2.quest_desc: ["为何要等待？哦,你有合理的理由等待？比如物品可能会消失.嗯,我没想到那些.\\n\\n使用&a延迟拾取拓展&f,&a真空模块&f会等待&a10游戏刻&f(每个拓展增加等待时间)才拾取掉落的物品!\\n&7[Why wait? Oh you have valid reasons for waiting? Like items that might despawn. Huh wasn't thinking about those. \\n\\nWith Pickup Delay Augment the Vacuum Module will wait 10 ticks with every Augment in it to pick up dropped items! ]&f"]
	quest.185074907753AE77.quest_desc: ["如果你在使用路由器,我希望你有一些游戏知识.\\n\\n以防万一,”销毁”一个物品意味着删除它.\\n\\n任何进入路由器的物品,都将被永久删除!\\n\\n建议配合过滤器使用这个...\\n&7[If you are using Routers I hope you have some game knowledge. \\n\\nJust incase, to void an Item means to delete it. \\n\\nAny items that come into the Router, will be deleted forever! \\n\\nRecommend using Filters with this one...]&f"]
	quest.1A806C1A54B26EB5.quest_desc: ["你不想让所有东西都在更大范围内行动吗？你希望你的真空模块在你的世界里留出一些空间来掉落物品？那么我想你可以缩小范围.\\n&7[You don't want everything to do their actions at a larger range? You want your Vacuum to leave some room for dropping items in your World? Then I guess you can range down.]&f"]
	quest.1AA81C41431FD145.quest_desc: ["拉..!拉..!拉..!\\n\\n拉取器是发送器的反面,它从容器中拉取物品到路由器的缓存.\\n\\n容器必须与路由器相邻.\\n&7[Pull..! Pull..! Pull..! \\n\\nThe Puller is the opposite of the Sender, it pulls items from Inventories into the Router's Buffer. \\n\\nThe Inventory has to be adjacent to the Router.]&f"]
	quest.20D4568857887D38.quest_desc: ["有时路由器可能处于危险境地,比如生成凋灵.\\n\\n为了保护它,你需要一个防爆升级.\\n\\nTNT炸不坏它,凋灵炸不坏它,只有你能.\\n&7[Sometimes a Router might be in a dangerous situation, like spawning a Wither. \\n\\nIn order to protect it you'll need a Blast Upgrade. \\n\\nTNT won't break it, Wither won't break it, only you.]&f"]
	quest.233C7CAA573D6045.quest_desc: ["模块决定了路由器执行的动作.\\n\\n它们可以让你的路由器从箱子中拉取物品,或将物品放入箱子,甚至两者兼得!还有更多功能!\\n\\n模块本身放入路由器,并且可以安装多个.\\n\\n过滤器和升级则放入模块本身.\\n&7[Modules determine the action the Router preforms.\\n\\nThey can make it so your Router pulls items from Chests, or put items into chests, or even both! And much more!\\n\\nModules go into the Router themselves and multiple can be installed.\\n\\nFiltering and Upgrades go into the Modules themselves.]&f"]
	quest.233C7CAA573D6045.title: "&l模块&7[lModules]&f"
	quest.2405663C033CBDF1.quest_desc: ["MK3不关心XYZ轴、视线或维度.\\n\\n只要容器在同一个Minecraft世界中,它就能将物品移入其中.\\n\\n见鬼,我甚至不确定容器是否必须在Minecraft游戏中才能发送!\\n&7[MK3 doesn't worry about XYZ axis, line of sight, or Dimension. \\n\\nAs long as the Inventory is in the same Minecraft World it can move items into it. \\n\\nHeck I'm not even sure if the Inventory has to be in the game of Minecraft to send to!]&f"]
	quest.2447208F1DC74FFE.quest_desc: ["路由器可能很吵,而且当你拥有数百个时,噪音肯定会叠加.\\n\\n投资消音升级可能是个好主意!\\n&7[Routers can be noisy, and noise definitely stacks when you have hundreds of them.\\n\\nMight be nice to invest in Muffer Upgrades then!]&f"]
	quest.247DAE5B4E1AC7F1.quest_desc: ["水进.\\n水出.\\n\\n&a流体模块&f会从路由器附近获取流体源并放入缓存中的储罐,或者从其缓存的储罐中取出流体并放置在其前方.\\n\\n仅对与路由器相邻的方块有效,如果你想要更大的范围,你需要...\\n&7[Water in. \\nWater out. \\n\\nThe Fluid Module will either take Liquid Sources from near the Router and put it into a Tank in the Buffer or take Liquid from a Tank in it's Buffer and place it in front of it. \\n\\nOnly works for adjacent blocks to the Router, if you want bigger range you'll need...]&f"]
	quest.2B60D123123A5E8E.quest_desc: ["为什么要设定能量可以去哪里？何不让它自由释放!\\n\\n就像释放一群蜜蜂,能量几乎会瞬间到达各处(嗡嗡声更少).附近任何需要能量的方块都会被无线充能.\\n&7[Why set a location to where the Energy can go? Why not let it go free! \\n\\nLike freeing a bunch of Bees, the Energy will go everywhere almost instantly (with less buzzing). Any blocks needing Energy nearby will be charged wirelessly.]&f"]
	quest.2BB5769119BA2472.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r为AllTheMods整合包创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&e保留所有权利&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.2DD5F0693780B10A.quest_desc: ["与挤压机MK2一起使用,挤压出的方块将模仿真实方块.&a红石块&f会发出红石信号,荧石会发光,草方块会表现得透明.但只有使用这个拓展时才行!\\n对熔炉或&a富集仓&f等方块实体无效.\\n&7[Used with the Extruder MK2, blocks extruded will mimic the actual blocks. Redstone Blocks will emit Redstone, Glowstone will emit light, Grass will act transparent. But only with this Augment! \\nDoesn't work with Block Entities like Furnaces or Enrichment Chambers.]&f"]
	quest.3025081DA6D2B398.quest_desc: ["通常路由器控制模块,但有了这个拓展,模块就失控了!AWOl!纯粹的无政府状态!\\n\\n它将监听自己的红石激活信号,而不是路由器的.\\n&7[Usually the Router commands the Modules but with this Augment the Module goes rouge! AWOl! Pure anarchy! \\n\\nIt will listen to it's own Redstone activation rather than the Routers.]&f"]
	quest.309B6B8368E535A0.quest_desc: ["路由器每次在其刻中执行一次动作.\\n\\n默认为20刻或1秒.\\n\\n这可以通过&a风驰&f升级减少刻数!\\n&7[A Router does it's action every time it has one of it's ticks. \\n\\nDefault is 20 Ticks or 1 Second. \\n\\nThis can be made to less Ticks with the Speed Upgrade!]&f"]
	quest.326C63F7DC713E71.quest_desc: ["分发器是发送器模块的同父异母兄弟.(确切地说,是MK2那边的MK3).\\n\\n它不是发送到一个容器,而是发送到多个选定的容器.\\n\\n它可以以多种模式发送:&a轮询&f、随机、最近优先或最远优先.&a轮询&f依次向每个容器发送等量物品,就像扑克牌发牌员.随机会随机选择一个容器输送.其他模式由与路由器的距离决定.\\n&7[The Distributer is the half siblings of the Sender Modules. (The MK3 to be exact, on the MK2 side). \\n\\nInstead of sending to 1 Inventory it will send to multiple that are selected. \\n\\nIt can send in multiple modes: Round Robin, Random, Nearest First, or Farthest First. Round Robin does an even amount to each in a row, like a dealer in Poker. Random will randomly choose an inventory to feed. The others are determined by the distance from the Router.]&f"]
	quest.346B9339E3D66478.quest_desc: ["能量几乎被所有东西使用,所以你几乎需要把它送到各处.幸好&a能量模块&f能帮上忙!\\n\\n&a能量模块&f会将推入其中的任何能量,移动到别处!移动到你所设定的任何地方!\\n&7[Energy is something used by practically everything so you need to send it almost everywhere. Thankfully the Energy Module will help with that! \\n\\nThe Energy Module will move any energy pushed into it, somewhere else! To wherever you set it to!]&f"]
	quest.36DED7099E80ED51.quest_desc: ["这个模块如其名,它放置方块.\\n\\n设置你想要放置方块的方向,最好设置过滤器,然后把模块和方块扔进路由器!一旦红石信号就绪,方块就会被放置!\\n&7[This one does as the name suggests, it places Blocks. \\n\\nSet the Direction you want the Block placed, preferably set the Filter, then throw the Module and Blocks into the Router! Once the Redstone is set the Blocks will be placed!]&f"]
	quest.37F2BE3C2BAF7C2D.quest_desc: ["标签是Minecraft的重要组成部分.\\n\\n对于所有不知道的人,它们作为一种组织工具,帮助为同一任务选择相似的物品.比如用任何木板制作工作台,或者用任何斧头最快地砍倒树木.\\n\\n要通过标签过滤,放入一个物品,然后从组中选择标签.比如&a铁矿石&f代表矿石.\\n&7[Tags are an essential part of Minecraft. \\n\\nFor all who don't know they work as an organization tool to help choose similar items for the same task. Like Crafting Table being made with any Planks or Trees being Chopped down fastest with any Axe. \\n\\nTo filter by Tag put an item in, then select the tag from the groups. Like Iron Ore for Ores.]&f"]
	quest.38954551309F42A7.quest_desc: ["发送器模块MK2与MK1类似,但限制更少.\\n\\nMK2不需要直接视线或位于同一XYZ轴上.\\n\\n但必须在同一维度,除非你有...\\n&7[Sender Module MK2 works similar to MK1 but with less restrictions. \\n\\nMK2 doesn't need direct line of sight or to be on same XYZ axis. \\n\\nWill have to be in the same Dimension though, unless you have...]&f"]
	quest.3C54C36CE97A48DC.quest_desc: ["投掷器投掷,\\n发射器发射,\\n而投掷模块投掷!\\n\\n&a投掷模块&f不会从缓存中好好放下物品,而是会扔出去？多远？由你决定!\\n&7[Droppers drop,\\nDispensers dispense, \\nAnd Flingers fling! \\n\\nInstead of nicely setting down items from the Buffer, the Flinger Module will throw them? How far? You determine that!]&f"]
	quest.40788326E791845D.quest_desc: ["挤压真是个古板的词.\\n\\n&a金属挤压机&f在收到&a红石信号&f时,会将路由器缓存中的方块在路由器前方排成一条线放置.当信号关闭时,它会破坏所有这些方块.\\n\\n对制作门很有用!\\n&7[Extrude is such a prude word. \\n\\nThe Extruder will place the blocks in the Router's Buffer in a line in front of the Router when given a Redstone Signal. When the Signal is disabled it will break all those blocks. \\n\\nUseful for Doors!]&f"]
	quest.417B88FEB1B8F44E.quest_desc: ["意思是这些模块会吸!字面意思!\\n\\n&a真空模块&f会吸起设定区域内的任何物品,并将它们移动到路由器的缓存.类似于&a吸收漏斗&f.\\n\\n也可与经验拓展一起使用!\\n&7[Mean these Suck! Literally! \\n\\nVacuum Module will suck up any items in the set area and move them to the Routers Buffer. Similar to the Absorption Hopper. \\n\\nAlso can be used with Experience Augment!]&f"]
	quest.475E1B94A61B9EB0.quest_desc: ["像MK1一样,这个模块会拉取!只是不仅从相邻的容器,而是从附近的任何容器!\\n&7[Like the MK1 this pulls! Just not only from adjacent Inventories, but any Inventory nearby!]&f"]
	quest.4A03A671757B2EBF.quest_desc: ["耐久度、&a流体储量&f、&a能量储量&f、附魔等级和&a食物营养价值&f都是我们可以用&a检测过滤器&f进行筛选的类别.\\n\\n然后我们选择是希望它大于、小于、等于,还是与数值混合.\\n\\n接着我们给出一个数值,点击加号按钮将其添加到过滤器中.\\n\\n这可以用来只保留高耐久度的工具或高&a食物营养价值&f的食物.\\n&7[Durability, Fluid Level, Energy Level, Enchantment Level, and Food Value are all categories we can use with Inspection Filter.\\n\\nThen we select if we want it Greater than, Lesser than, Equal to, or a mix of those with the Numbered Amount.\\n\\nNext we give it a Numbered Amount and hit the Plus Button to add it to the Filter.\\n\\nThis can be used to only keep Tools with high Durability or Food with high Food Value.]&f"]
	quest.4CC963F5AECF285A.quest_desc: ["通常路由器每个刻移动1个物品.这可以通过堆叠升级翻倍并叠加!\\n\\n1个堆叠升级是2个物品,2个堆叠是4个物品,6个堆叠是每秒64个物品.\\n&7[Normally the Router moves 1 item each of it's Ticks. This can be doubled and stacked! with the Stack Upgrade. \\n\\n1 Stack Upgrade is 2 Items, 2 Stacks 4 Items, and 6 Stacks is 64 Items a second.]&f"]
	quest.4EAFE7B240AF0A4D.quest_desc: ["就是够不到你需要的东西？试试范围扩大!\\n\\n有了这个,所有东西都会在更远的距离执行它们的动作.真空模块拾取物品的范围更大.能量传输更远.投掷模块投掷更有力!\\n&7[Just can't reach what you need to? Try Ranging Up! \\n\\nWith this everything will do their actions but farther. Vacuum has higher range for picking up items. Energy goes farther. Flinger flings with more strength!]&f"]
	quest.4FA5192164E4A427.quest_desc: ["流体不像物品那样堆叠,所以它的升级有点不同.仍然移动更多,只是速率不同.\\n&7[Fluid doesn't stack like Items do, so its upgrade is a little different. Still moves more just at a different rate.]&f"]
	quest.53A5F5E49EA8D5AF.quest_desc: [
		"这里有一个使用&d模块化路由器&f制作超级简单、有条理的&a怪物农场&f的好例子.(不包括杀死怪物的方法).\\n\\n为此,我将以&a凋灵骷髅&f农场为例.\\n\\n首先,你想用&a真空模块&f将物品吸入缓存.接下来,用&a销毁模块&f处理掉&a石剑&f.为确保它不删除所有东西,使用一个包含&a石剑&f且不匹配&a伤害&f的白名单过滤器.之后,你需要一个地方存放战利品,我推荐抽屉系统.然后,使用发送器模块将战利品发送到存储系统.\\n\\n这就是你所需要的全部!\\n&7[Here's a good example of using Modular Routers to make a super easy organized Mob Farm. (Does not include way of killing mobs). \\n\\nFor it I'll use a Wither Skeleton Farm as example. \\n\\nFirst, you want to get Items into the Buffer with a Vacuum Module. Next, get rid of the Stone Swords with a Void Module. To make sure it doesn't delete everything use a Whitelist Filter with the Stone Sword in it and not matching Damage. After, that you'll need a place to put the Loot, I recommend a Drawer System. Then, use a Sender Module to send the Loot to the Storage System. \\n\\nThat's all you need!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/router/router_mob.png width:200 height:65 align:center}"
	]
	quest.53A5F5E49EA8D5AF.title: "用于&a怪物农场&f的路由器&7[Routers for Mob Farms]&f"
	quest.53B58FC3958750E7.quest_desc: ["你把玩放置器太多,需要破坏那些方块了吗？\\n\\n它的等级和附魔由制作它的镐决定.\\n\\n现在设定区域,最好放一个过滤器,然后让它运行!\\n\\n&a可与&f放置器一起使用,做诸如将矿石变成物品之类的事情.\\n&7[Did you play around with the Placer too much and need to Break those Blocks? \\n\\nIts Tier and Enchants are determined by the Pickaxe its Crafted with. \\n\\nNow set the area and hopefully put a Filter and let it run! \\n\\nCan be used with a Placer to do stuff like turning Ores into Items.]&f"]
	quest.553C44F85E508DE3.quest_desc: ["这个很独特,因为它不只用于一个路由器,而是用于多个.\\n\\n如果你想让多个路由器同时工作,那么每个都需要一个同步升级.\\n\\n需要在它自己的GUI中调谐.\\n&7[This one is unique as it's not used for just 1 Router but for multiple. \\n\\nIf you want multiple Routers working at the same time then each needs a Sync Upgrade. \\n\\nWill need to be tuned in its own GUI.]&f"]
	quest.5560F303C452E110.quest_desc: ["&a金属挤压机&f推动方块和实体,但为什么不推得更远些呢!\\n\\n是实体,不是方块.\\n&7[The Extruder pushes blocks and entities by why not push it some more! \\n\\nThe entities not the blocks.]&f"]
	quest.5FB29F3F4DF17765.quest_desc: ["有时你不想让每个模块一次移动多个堆叠,所以当你只想让1个模块这样做时,使用一个拓展!但这不能与升级叠加...实际上它会覆盖它们.\\n&7[Sometimes you don't want every Module to move multiple stacks at a time, so when you just want 1 Modules to do so use an Augment! This does not stack with Upgrades though... infact it overrides them.]&f"]
	quest.6063F4B7BE4D394C.quest_desc: ["&a发送器&f模块会将路由器缓存槽中的物品移动到另一个容器中.\\n\\nMK1只会将物品移动到与路由器在同一XYZ轴上且有直接视线的容器中.如果有方块阻挡,MK1发送器将不会发送.\\n&7[The Sender Modules will move Items in the Router's Buffer Slot into another Inventory. \\n\\nMK1 will only move items into Inventories on the same XYZ axis as the Router and with direct line of sight. If there is a block in the way, the MK1 Sender will not send.]&f"]
	quest.63E4529AF8894018.quest_desc: ["&l&d模块化路由器&f&r是一个物流模组.\\n\\n一切都从路由器开始!所以做一个吧!\\n\\n另外,缓存是路由器中单个物品槽,物品将通过它进出.大多数模块工作需要红石信号.\\n&7[lModular Routers is a logistics mod. \\n\\nIt all starts with the Router! So make one! \\n\\nAlso the Buffer is the single item slot in the Router where items will come and go through. And it will need Redstone signal for most modules to work.]&f"]
	quest.63E4529AF8894018.title: "&l&d模块化路由器&f&7[lModular Routers]&f"
	quest.6648BC7D14233006.quest_desc: ["拓展类似于升级,但是针对单个模块的!\\n&7[Augments are similar to Upgrades but for the individual Modules!]&f"]
	quest.6648BC7D14233006.title: "&l拓展&7[lAugments]&f"
	quest.674F28BCA2E4A3C8.quest_desc: ["移动物品时,路由器可能会变得相当贪婪,把它们肮脏的天线能碰到的每一个物品都拿走!\\n\\n使用&a调节拓展&f,你可以限制移动的数量.\\n&7[When moving items Routers can get pretty greedy, taking every single item they can get their grubby antennas on! \\n\\nWith Regulator Augment you can limit how much is moved.]&f"]
	quest.6B747129A85AA768.quest_desc: ["现在更像&a吸收漏斗&f了!\\n\\n&a真空模块&f现在也会拾取&a经验球&f以及物品.你如何处理经验取决于你!\\n&7[Now even more like the Absorption Hopper! \\n\\nVacuum Module will now pickup XP Orbs as well as Items. Whatever you do with the XP is up to you!]&f"]
	quest.6E5954C257726F86.quest_desc: ["按模组过滤会非常有帮助.\\n\\n要使用它,放入来自某个模组的物品,然后它会显示模组名称,点击加号按钮将其添加!\\n&7[Filtering per mod can be very helpful.\\n\\nTo use it, put an item in from a certain mod, then it will show the mod name, and hit the Plus button to add it!]&f"]
	quest.71A1FD0772453B51.quest_desc: ["你是不是很讨厌&a右键点击&f所有东西？从用剪刀剪羊毛到用桶挤牛奶？都21世纪了,我们应该让机器人来做所有事!或者至少让路由器来处理一切.\\n\\n使用&a执行模块&f,它会像你一样&a右键点击&f物品.\\n\\n你可以设置它要&a右键点击&f什么,是攻击还是使用生物或方块,是否按住潜行键&a右键点击&f,以及在模块中设置它们需要多近的距离.\\n&7[Don't you hate Right Clicking everything? From Sheep with Shears to Cows with Buckets? It's the 21st Century we should have Robots to everything! Or atleast Routers do everything. \\n\\nWith Activator Module it will act as if it were you Right Clicking things. \\n\\nYou can set what it will Right Click, if it will Attack or Use the Mob or Block, if you Shift Right Click, and how close they need to be in the Module.]&f"]
	quest.71FDF8CD953E46FC.quest_desc: ["哈哈,我用任务里的创造模式物品吓到你了吗？\\n\\n别担心,完成本章你不需要那个物品,我只是想吓唬你一下\\n\\n我有时候也可以找点乐子……\\n&7[HAHAHA did I scare you with the Creative item in the quests?\\n\\nDon't worry you won't need the item to finish this chapter, I just wanted to scare you\\n\\nI can have fun sometimes...]&f"]
	quest.72A71E1D6D8996FD.quest_desc: ["这是代码吗？我又不是程序员!？我只是想写这些任务!\\n\\n在这里,你可以在&a搜索栏&f中输入正则表达式,然后点击加号按钮将其添加到过滤器中.每当该正则表达式出现时,它就会被过滤掉.\\n&7[Is this code? I'm not a coder!? I just wanted to make these quests! \\n\\nHere you can type in a Regex into the Search Bar and click the Plus Button to add it to the Filter. Whenever that Regex comes up it will be filtered out.]&f"]
	quest.73D60868024FF907.quest_desc: ["流体MK2!\\n\\n附近的任何液体源都可以用这个模块处理,不仅仅是相邻的.\\n&7[The Fluid MK2! \\n\\nAny Liquid Source nearby can be used with this one, not just adjacent.]&f"]
	quest.75FE0B514448865B.quest_desc: ["升级模块直接放入路由器中,路由器最多可以容纳5个.升级模块会直接影响所有适用的模块,并且通常可以叠加!\\n&7[Upgrades go directly into the Router and the Router can hold 5 of them. Upgrades directly affect all Modules that they can and usually can stack!]&f"]
	quest.75FE0B514448865B.title: "&l升级模块&7[lUpgrades]&f"
	quest.76062D375E4CC8DD.quest_desc: ["我们见过过滤器,也见过&a轮询&f,现在我们把两者结合起来!这对于保持物品按特定顺序排列很有用,比如制作&d神秘农业&f种子时!\\n&7[We've seen Filters and we've seen Round Robins, now we're seeing both! This is useful for keeping the Items in a select order like for when making Mystical Agriculture Seeds!]&f"]
	quest.7F8DEDD0A54D1E11.quest_desc: ["我在想投掷器是做什么的？\\n我觉得它们是用来扔东西的……\\n\\n缓冲区中的任何物品都会被扔到地上.\\n\\n可能对像&d植物魔法&f这样的模组有帮助!\\n&7[I wonder what Droppers do? \\nI think they drop things... \\n\\nAny item in the Buffer will be dropped on the ground. \\n\\nCould be helpful with something like Botania!]&f"]
	task.3007461CFCC0A013.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.41EEE559F6402D81.title: "&a创造模块&f&7[Creative Module]&f"
	task.631388151555159B.title: "发送模块&7[Sender Modules]&f"
	task.76EEAE9313F68334.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.00A6020BC979947F.quest_desc: ["用你刚刚召唤的&9巨灵粉碎者&r,你可以分解一个&a回响碎片&f和一个&a艾瑟金属锭&f,当它们与&a荧光墨囊&f结合时,就能制作出&a青色粉笔&f.\\n&7[With your freshly summoned Marid Crusher, you can break down an Echo Shard and an Iesnium Ingot, which when combined with a Glow Ink Sac creates Cyan Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.00A6020BC979947F.title: "&3&a青色粉笔&f&7[Cyan Chalk]&f"
	quest.03250A0202C25E80.quest_desc: ["在你成功击败了用&4提比拉的吸引&r召唤的&9无束缚巨灵&r恶魔后,你可以用它掉落的&9巨灵精华&r来制作”最高”等级的彩色粉笔,&a蓝色粉笔&f.\\n&7[After you've successfully slain the Unbound Marid Demon that you summoned with Tibira's Attraction, you can use the Marid Essence that it drops to craft the \"highest\" colored Chalk, Blue Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.03250A0202C25E80.title: "&9&a蓝色粉笔&f&7[Blue Chalk]&f"
	quest.08697EB269B011FD.quest_desc: [
		"使用&d罗纳扎的接触&r,你可以将你的&b艾瑟&a献祭之碗&f&r升级为邪术圣杯.在仪式中使用时,能完全减少仪式完成所需的时间.\\n&7[With Ronaza's Contact, you can upgrade your Iesnium Sacrificial Bowl to the Eldritch Chalice. When used in a ritual, reduces the time it takes to complete... entirely. ]&f"
		""
		"是的,邪术圣杯能让所有仪式瞬间完成!\\n&7[Yes, the Eldritch Chalice makes it so that all rituals complete instantly!]&f"
	]
	quest.08697EB269B011FD.title: "邪术圣杯&7[Eldritch Chalice]&f"
	quest.0A25276925EB0CBA.quest_desc: [
		"一旦你收集齐了所有颜色的粉笔和基础粉笔,你就可以进行第二种&d无需恶魔&r类型的仪式,&d罗纳扎的接触&r.这是终极仪式,用到了你迄今为止学到的一切!\\n&7[Once you've gathered every single colored Chalk and Foundation Chalk, you can perform the second Demon-less type ritual, Ronaza's Contact. This is the ultimate ritual, using everything you've learned so far!]&f"
		""
		"它有使用次数限制,但用这个仪式创造的每样东西都超级强大!\\n&7[It has limited uses, but everything created with this ritual is super powerful!]&f"
	]
	quest.0A25276925EB0CBA.quest_subtitle: "凭此圣物,我召唤……&7[With this sacred treasure I summon...]&f"
	quest.0A25276925EB0CBA.title: "&d罗纳扎的接触&7[Ronaza's Contact]&f"
	quest.0B3EA604C5172D98.quest_desc: [
		"为了指定我们想要召唤哪个&c&m恶魔&r &9朋友&r,我们需要制作一本特定的&b束缚之书&r.\\n\\n要制作这个,你需要在&d灵火&r中净化一些&a黑色染料&f来获得&a纯净墨水&f.有了这个,我们将制作我们的第一本束缚之书,它将召唤一个&a小魔&r恶魔.\\n&7[For us to specify which Demon Friend we want to summon, we'll need to make a specific Book of Binding.\\n\\nTo make this, you'll need to purify some Black Dye in Spiritfire to get Purified Ink. With this, we're going to make our first Book of Binding which will summon a Foliot Demon.]&f"
		""
		"或者,你也可以制作一本空的束缚之书,之后可以根据你需要的仪式等级进行染色.\\n&7[Alternatively, you can make an Empty Book of Binding, which can be dyed later to fit whatever tier of ritual you need.]&f"
	]
	quest.0B3EA604C5172D98.title: "&b&d束缚之书&7[Books of Binding]&f"
	quest.0BD6365534BF04D5.quest_desc: [
		"有了&a黄绿色粉笔&f,是时候深入&5附身仪式&r了.这些仪式与其他仪式略有不同,因为它们都需要活祭品,通常是小型生物,如鸡、蜜蜂、蝙蝠等.然而,随着仪式变得更加复杂,它们将需要越来越大的祭品.\\n&7[With Lime Chalk, it's time to delve into Possession Rituals. These rituals are slightly different from the others because they all require a live sacrifice, usually small mobs such as Chickens, Bees, Bats, etc. However, as rituals get more complicated, they will require larger and larger sacrifices. ]&f"
		""
		"即使你已经将所有需要的物品和束缚之书放入了&a黄金献祭之碗&f,&a魔法仪式&f也不会开始,除非你在符文上杀死祭品.\\n&7[Even if you've placed all of the items needed and the Book of Binding into the Golden Sacrificial Bowl, the Ritual will not begin until you kill the sacrifice on top of the runes.]&f"
		""
		"建议你制作一些生物捕捉物品,比如空灵魂宝石、罐子、&a生物捕捉工具&f,或者&a量子捕捉器&f!\\n&7[It is recommended that you make some sort of mob capture item such as an Empty Soul Gem, Jar, Mob Imprisonment Tool, or Quantum Catcher!]&f"
		""
		"&5附身仪式&r的第一级是&e海德林的引诱&r,它只用于获取普通物品,如&a骷髅头颅&f和末地石.因此,你可以直接跳到第二级仪式,&a伊哈甘的奴役&r.\\n&7[The first tier of Possession rituals is Heidryn's Lure, which is only used to get mundane items like Skeleton Skulls and End Stone. Because of this, you can skip straight to the second tier of ritual, Ihagan's Enthrallment. ]&f"
	]
	quest.0BD6365534BF04D5.quest_subtitle: "你要召唤谁？&7[Who you gonna call?]&f"
	quest.0BD6365534BF04D5.title: "&a伊哈甘的奴役&7[Ihagan's Enthrallment]&f"
	quest.0C554FD9A150D2CD.quest_desc: [
		"你也可以使用&c铜&a献祭之碗&f&r和&c银&a献祭之碗&f!&r\\n&7[You can also use Copper Sacrificial Bowls and Silver Sacrificial Bowls!]&f"
		""
		"虽然这些纯粹是为了装饰,功能上没有任何改变,但它们看起来确实漂亮多了!\\n&7[While these are purely for decoration and change nothing functionally, they do look much nicer!]&f"
	]
	quest.0D18BBB04693885A.quest_desc: ["斯特里吉欧的高等束缚是&6灌注仪式&r的第二级.它用于许多不同的事情,但我们主要需要的是&a灌注镐&f和灰色糊剂.\\n&7[Strigeor's Higher Binding is the second tier of Infusion Rituals. It's used for many different things, but the main things we'll need are the Infused Pickaxe and Gray Paste.]&f"]
	quest.0D18BBB04693885A.quest_subtitle: "”万物”仪式&7[The \"Everything\" Ritual]&f"
	quest.0D18BBB04693885A.title: "&a斯特里吉欧的高等束缚&7[Strigeor's Higher Binding]&f"
	quest.0FE3094B22412BD3.quest_desc: ["&a献祭祭坛&f是神秘学提供的另一个工具,这次专注于献祭的自动化.\\n\\n这个祭坛放在你的中心碗下方,如果附近有一个装有潜在祭品的禁锢罐,它将允许用附近&a魔源罐&f中的源质来替代献祭.\\n&7[The Sacrificial Altar is another tool Ars Ocultas offers, this time, focusing on the automation of Sacrifices.\\n\\nThis Altar goes under your central bowl, and will allow for Sacrifices to be substituted with Source from a nearby Source Jar, if a Containment Jar containing the would-be sacrifice is also nearby]&f"]
	quest.0FE3094B22412BD3.quest_subtitle: "源质替代献祭&7[Source Substitutes Sacrifice]&f"
	quest.11A0593C0E2E6A35.quest_desc: ["使用&e埃兹维乌斯的灵体强制&r,我们可以将多种不同的自然方块注入能量,形成一些&2自然糊剂&r.将这种糊剂与一些&a含杂白色粉笔&f结合,就能制作出&a绿色粉笔&f.\\n&7[Using Eziveus' Spectral Compulsion, we can imbue a myriad of different nature blocks to form some Nature Paste. Combine this Paste with some Impure White Chalk to create Green Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.11A0593C0E2E6A35.title: "&2&a绿色粉笔&f&7[Green Chalk]&f"
	quest.145C8235BCCB9BA8.quest_desc: [
		"如果我们想收集所有的粉笔,我们需要召唤并杀死一个不太友好的&c炎魔&r.\\n&7[If we want to collect all of the Chalks, we'll need to summon and kill aa not-so friendly Afrit.]&f"
		""
		"尽管这不是一个&5附身仪式&r,但这个仪式你需要一个活祭品.在这个例子中,我们将献祭一头牛.对不起了贝琪!\\n&7[Even though this isn't a Possession Ritual, you'll need a live sacrifice for this ritual. In this instance, we'll be sacrificing a Cow. Sorry Betsy!]&f"
	]
	quest.145C8235BCCB9BA8.quest_subtitle: "安息吧,贝琪&7[R.I.P. Betsy]&f"
	quest.145C8235BCCB9BA8.title: "&c&a红色粉笔&f&7[Red Chalk]&f"
	quest.172D2A634E849562.quest_desc: ["凭借我们收获&c艾瑟金属&r的能力,我们可以召唤恶魔来为我们采矿……我是说……帮我们收集矿石.绝对不是剥削恶魔什么的.\\n\\n为此,我们需要创建一个&d&a维度矿井&f&r来进入恶魔采矿世界.你还需要一个被禁锢在灯里的采矿恶魔,你把它放在矿井里才能工作.虽然任何等级的恶魔都能完成这个任务,但等级越高,工作速度越快,为你开采艾瑟金属的几率也越高.\\n\\n&a矿井&f不会自动输出物品.你需要使用漏斗、运输恶魔或其他方法(如物品管道)将物品提取出来.如果超过存储限制,它会销毁多余的物品.\\n&7[With our ability to harvest Iesnium, we can call upon the Demons to do our bidding in the mines... I mean.... help us gather ores. Definitely not exploiting Demons or anything.\\n\\nFor this, we'll need to create a Dimensional Mineshaft to access the Demon Mining World. You'll also need a Mining Demon confined to a lamp, which you'll place inside of the Mineshaft for it to work. While any tier will complete this quest, higher tiers work faster and have a higher chance at mining Iesnium for you.\\n\\nThe Mineshafts do not auto-export on their own. You will need to extract the items out using either Hoppers, Transporting Demons, or some other method like Item Pipes. It will void any items over its storage limit.]&f"]
	quest.172D2A634E849562.title: "&c恶魔采矿&7[Demon Mining]&f"
	quest.1848F431D0380DA9.quest_desc: [
		"类似于&a斯特里吉欧的高等束缚&r的粉笔修复功能,&c塞维拉的永久禁锢&r可以利用炎魔的力量来修复物品.\\n&7[Similar to the Chalk Repairing function of Strigeor's Higher Binding, Sevira's Permanent Confinement can be used to repair items using the power of an Afrit Demon.]&f"
		""
		"这个仪式可以修复几乎任何东西,所以&e采矿恶魔&f、工具和盔甲都可以恢复到原来的耐久度!\\n&7[This ritual can repair just about anything, so Demon Miners, tools, and armor can all be restored to their original durability! ]&f"
		""
		"所有用这个仪式修复的物品都会保留其原始属性(词缀、附魔等),所以不用担心你珍贵的附魔!\\n&7[All items that are repaired using this ritual retain their original properties (affixes, enchantments, etc), so don't worry about your precious enchantments!]&f"
	]
	quest.1848F431D0380DA9.quest_subtitle: "免费(差不多)的耐久度!&7[Free(ish) durability!]&f"
	quest.1848F431D0380DA9.title: "修复物品&7[Repairing Items]&f"
	quest.1B5177A774FCEF64.quest_desc: ["在我们开始寻求恶魔朋友的帮助之前,我们需要制作仪式最重要的物品:&a粉笔&r.\\n\\n需要几种颜色的粉笔,更高级的仪式需要多种粉笔才能激活.首先,&b&a白色粉笔&f&r是最容易获得的.\\n\\n先把异界石扔进熔炉,再把异界原木扔进&d灵火&r.用你创造的物品,你就能制作出&a含杂白色粉笔&f.\\n\\n要净化任何一块粉笔,只需把它扔进&d灵火&r中清洗.使用&a纯化&f后的粉笔在地上画会画出&m恶魔的&r漂亮符号.这些符号很难&a移除&f,除非你给自己做个&a&a粉笔擦&f&r.做吧,值得的.\\n&7[Before we start enlisting the help of our Demon friends, we will need to create the most important item needed for Rituals: Chalk.\\n\\nThere are several colors of chalk needed, with higher level Rituals requiring several to activate. To start with, White Chalk is the easiest to get.\\n\\nStart by tossing Otherstone in a furnace, and tossing Otherworld Logs into Spiritfire. With the items you create, you'll be able to make the Impure White Chalk.\\n\\nTo purify any piece of Chalk, simply throw it into Spiritfire to cleanse it. Using the Purified Chalk on the ground will draw demonic pretty symbols on the ground. These are a pain to remove, unless of course, you make yourself the Chalk Brush. Do it, it's worth it.]&f"]
	quest.1B5177A774FCEF64.title: "准备仪式:&e粉笔&7[Preparing for a Ritual: Chalk]&f"
	quest.1BDB369FD243D4C6.quest_desc: [
		"可以说是你在&d神秘学&f中可以创造的最有用的物品,&b艾瑟金属砧&r是原版铁砧的超强版本.\\n&7[Arguably the most useful item that you can create in Occultism, the Iesnium Anvil is a super-powerful version of the Vanilla Anvil.]&f"
		""
		"使用&9乌菲克斯斯的倒置之塔&r创造,它:\\n&7[Created using Uphyxes' Inverted Tower, it:]&f"
		""
		"- 无法破坏.\\n&7[- Is unbreakable.]&f"
		"- 将任何在其上合成的物品的所有附魔最高等级提高一级.\\n&7[- Increases the maximum level of all enchants for anything combined on it by one level.]&f"
		"- 消耗的经验值是预估的一半(向下取整,所以如果显示25,则消耗12).\\n&7[- Costs half as much xp as the estimate says (rounded down, so if it says 25, it'll cost 12).]&f"
		"- 对同一物品进行重复编辑时,经验值要求增加得更少.\\n&7[- Has a smaller experience requirement increase for repeated edits on the same item.]&f"
		"- 提高了可以编辑物品的最高经验等级(即显示”过于昂贵!”的那个点).\\n&7[- Increases the maximum xp level at which you can edit items (the point at which it says \"Too Expensive!\").]&f"
	]
	quest.1DE0F289821F55D1.quest_desc: ["现在我们有了一个小魔粉碎者,我们可以&m使用&r礼貌地请它为我们粉碎一些&e末地石&r、&9黑曜石&r和&7方解石&r.我们将用这些来制作一些新的粉笔!\\n&7[Now that we have a Foliot Crusher, we can use politely ask it to crush down some End Stone, Obsidian and Calcite for us. We'll use these to make some new Chalk!]&f"]
	quest.1DE0F289821F55D1.title: "&a粉笔升级&7[Chalking It Up]&f"
	quest.1EB887F8072439A3.quest_desc: ["在使用&9法特玛的激励吸引&r召唤&9巨灵粉碎者&r或使用&a奥菲克斯的呼唤&r召唤&a巨灵粉碎者&r之后,你可以将冰、&a浮冰&f和&a蓝冰&f粉碎成它们的粉碎形态,并用这些来制作&a淡蓝色粉笔&f.\\n&7[After using either Fatma's Incentivized Attraction to summon a Marid Crusher or Ophyx' Calling to summon a Djinni Crusher, you can turn Ice, Packed Ice, and Blue Ice into their crushed forms, and use these to create Light Blue Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.1EB887F8072439A3.title: "&b&a淡蓝色粉笔&f&7[Light Blue Chalk]&f"
	quest.2960FFE0C53DFEB1.quest_desc: [
		"&c塞维拉的永久禁锢&r是&6灌注仪式&r的第三级.它主要用于制作下一级的基础粉笔,&a黑色粉笔&f.\\n&7[Sevira's Permanent Confinement is the third tier of Infusion Rituals. It's mainly used to create the next level of foundation Chalk, Black Chalk.]&f"
		""
		"它还用于创造一些可以显著加快仪式制作和执行速度的物品.\\n&7[It's also used to create a couple of items that can speed up ritual making and performing by a significant amount.]&f"
	]
	quest.2960FFE0C53DFEB1.quest_subtitle: "”更多万物”仪式&7[The \"Even More Everything\" Ritual]&f"
	quest.2960FFE0C53DFEB1.title: "&c塞维拉的永久禁锢&7[Sevira's Permanent Confinement]&f"
	quest.29C83B00AC4AFC23.quest_desc: [
		"既然你已经走了这么远,你可能会问自己,接下来呢？嗯,在&d神秘学&f中还有更多东西可以探索!\\n&7[Now that you've come this far, you may be asking yourself, what's next? Well, there are so many more things to explore in Occultism! ]&f"
		""
		"你可以在你的&6&a魔灵全典&f&r中看到每个仪式和物品的完整列表,你可以尝试浏览所有仪式的成果,看看是否能找到让你感兴趣的东西!\\n&7[You can see a comprehensive list of every single ritual and item in your Dictionary of Spirits, you could try going through all the rituals' outcomes to see if you can find something that piques your interest!]&f"
		""
		"如果你还没有,你可以布置并装饰三个独立的仪式区域,一个用于召唤,一个用于附身,一个用于灌注.\\n&7[If you haven't already, you could lay out and decorate three separate ritual areas, one for Summons, one for Possessions, and one for Infusions.]&f"
		""
		"总有新的方法来利用每一个看似普通的功能,以最大化你在整合包中的体验.祝仪式制作愉快!\\n&7[There's always new ways to use each and every seemingly mundane feature to maximize your experience with the modpack. Happy ritual crafting!]&f"
	]
	quest.29C83B00AC4AFC23.title: "接下来呢？&7[What's Next?]&f"
	quest.2A3D132CDBDC8174.quest_desc: ["你可能想知道:为什么&d新生魔艺&f的物品会出现在&d神秘学&f章节中？这是因为我们有神秘学来连接这两个模组.特别是,灵体,比如我们的小魔粉碎者,可以在这些罐子里工作.你甚至可以把物品用管道输送到罐子里让灵体与之互动,它们会将物品输出到相邻的容器中(我发现罐子底部是最可靠的输出位置).如果它们无法输出到容器,就会把物品输出到世界上.\\n&7[You might be wondering: Why is an Ars Nouveau item in the Occultism chapter? That's because we have Ars Ocultas, to bridge the two mods. Particularly, Spirits, like our Foliot Crusher, can work in these jars. You can even pipe items into the jars for the spirits to interact with, and they will output it to adjacent inventories (I found the bottom side of the jar to be the most reliable place they output to). If they cannot output to an inventory, they'll output the items into the world.]&f"]
	quest.2A3D132CDBDC8174.quest_subtitle: "灵体可以在禁锢罐中工作&7[Spirits can work in Containment Jars]&f"
	quest.2A3D132CDBDC8174.title: "神秘学:&a精魂罐&f&7[Ars Ocultas: Spirit Jars]&f"
	quest.2A5004EB99AE4F96.quest_desc: [
		"还有更多异界物品需要收集,而每次需要&7&a第三只眼&f&r效果时都吃&c恶魔梦之果&r很烦人.\\n&7[There are more Otherworld items you will need to gather, and eating Demon's Dream Fruit every time you need the Third Eye effect gets annoying.]&f"
		""
		"这就是&d异界护目镜&r的用途!当装备时(即使放在饰品栏),它会提供&a第三只眼&f效果!\\n&7[This is what the Otherworld Goggles are for! When equipped (even in your Curios slot), it gives the Third Eye effect!]&f"
	]
	quest.2A5004EB99AE4F96.quest_subtitle: "别再吃那个水果了!&7[Quit eating that fruit!]&f"
	quest.2A5004EB99AE4F96.title: "行业工具:灵体护目镜&7[Tools of the Trade: Spectral Goggles]&f"
	quest.2A6FE386DF0E1D98.quest_desc: ["不想用&b&a淡蓝色粉笔&f&r召唤&9玛瑞德粉碎者&r？那你也可以用&a镇尼粉碎者&r凑合一下.&a奥菲克斯的召唤&r用于召唤&a镇尼&r.这包括恶魔妻子/丈夫.&a镇尼&r粉碎矿石的效率比弗利奥特高,但不如&c阿弗里特&r或&9玛瑞德&r.它们还能在不融化冰的情况下粉碎冰块.\\n&7[Don't want to get a Marid Crusher for Light Blue Chalk? Then you can settle for a Djinni Crusher instead. Ophyx' Calling is used for summoning Djinnis. This includes a Demonic Wife/Husband. Djinnis are able to crush ores more efficiently than Foliots, but not as efficiently as Afrits or Marids. They're also capable of crushing ice without melting it.]&f"]
	quest.2A6FE386DF0E1D98.quest_subtitle: "&a淡蓝色&f的替代路径&7[An alternate path for light blue]&f"
	quest.2A6FE386DF0E1D98.title: "&a奥菲克斯的召唤&7[Ophyx' Calling]&f"
	quest.2AD68066C1948C90.quest_desc: [
		"第一个&e弗利奥特粉碎者&r很酷,但如果我告诉你,你可以召唤一个恶魔,它能将每个原始矿石粉碎成6份粉末呢？\\n&7[That first Foliot Crusher was cool, but what if I told you that you could summon a demon that gives you 6 dusts per raw ore it crushes?]&f"
		""
		"&9玛瑞德粉碎者&r正是如此.要召唤一个,你需要使用&9法特玛的激励吸引&r.\\n&7[The Marid Crusher does exactly that. To summon one, you'll need to use Fatma's Incentivized Attraction. ]&f"
	]
	quest.2AD68066C1948C90.quest_subtitle: "最高级召唤&7[Maximum Summon]&f"
	quest.2AD68066C1948C90.title: "&9法特玛的激励吸引&7[Fatma's Incentivized Attraction]&f"
	quest.2CF96A264EB5522C.quest_desc: [
		"&9乌菲克西斯的倒置之塔&r是&6灌注仪式&r的最高等级.它不像其他三个等级那样用途广泛,但对于&d神秘学&f的”终局”来说仍然是必要的.\\n&7[Uphyxes' Inverted Tower is the maximum tier of Infusion Rituals. It doesn't have as many uses as the other three tiers, but it's still necessary for the \"endgame\" of Occultism. ]&f"
		""
		"它主要用于制造龙尘粉末,这是&a品红色粉笔&f的主要成分.\\n&7[Mainly, it's used to create Dragonyst Dust, which is the main ingredient for Magenta Chalk.]&f"
	]
	quest.2CF96A264EB5522C.quest_subtitle: "最高级灌注&7[Maximum Infusion]&f"
	quest.2CF96A264EB5522C.title: "&9乌菲克西斯的倒置之塔&7[Uphyxes' Inverted Tower]&f"
	quest.2E68E1D96B25336D.quest_desc: ["在击败几个由&6阿布拉斯的开放命令召唤&r召唤的恶魔附身&a僵尸猪灵&f后,你可以用它们掉落的恶魔肉来制作一些&a粉红色粉笔&f.\\n&7[After fighting through a few Demon Possessed Zombified Piglins summoned by Abras' Open Commanding Conjure, you can use the Demonic Meat dropped by them to craft some Pink Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.2E68E1D96B25336D.title: "&d&a粉红色粉笔&f&7[Pink Chalk]&f"
	quest.2FD22502E6481269.quest_desc: ["使用&d罗纳扎的联系&r,你可以升级你的灵魂宝石,制造一个三位一体宝石.它基本上就是灵魂宝石的强化版,可以捕捉更大的敌人,尽管它仍然无法容纳大多数Boss.\\n&7[Using Ronaza's Contact, you can upgrade your Soul Gem to create a Trinity Gem. It's basically just a beefed up version of the Soul Gem that can capture larger enemies, although it still can't contain most bosses.]&f"]
	quest.2FD22502E6481269.title: "三位一体宝石&7[Trinity Gem]&f"
	quest.30C5B597610F4AFB.quest_desc: ["使用埃兹维乌斯的灵质强制制造的第一个也是最重要的物品是研究碎片粉末.这需要与一些粉碎的绿宝石结合,来制造&a黄绿色粉笔&f!\\n&7[The first and most important item to make using Eziveus' Spectral Compulsion is the Research Fragment Dust. This is used in combination with some crushed Emeralds to create Lime Chalk!]&f"]
	quest.30C5B597610F4AFB.title: "&a&a黄绿色粉笔&f&7[Lime Chalk]&f"
	quest.33106E24A3B5DDD8.quest_desc: [
		"你旅程的下一步将是寻找&c艾瑟尼姆&r.\\n&7[The next step in your journey will be to find Iesnium.]&f"
		""
		"通常,你需要在&a下界&f洞穴探险,但这是一个空岛整合包!\\n&7[Normally, you would have to go spelunking in the Nether, but this is a Skyblock modpack!]&f"
		""
		"相反,尝试在&a远古残骸&f上使用&a原子再构机&f.\\n&7[Instead, try using an Atomic Reconstructor on Ancient Debris.]&f"
	]
	quest.33106E24A3B5DDD8.title: "&c艾瑟尼姆:异界矿石&7[Iesnium: Ore of the Otherworld]&f"
	quest.3543563DF036D461.quest_desc: ["要制造龙尘粉末,你需要进行&9乌菲克西斯的倒置之塔&r仪式.然而,要制造&a品红色粉笔&f,你还需要一些只能通过&9玛瑞德粉碎者&r获得的材料.\\n&7[To create Dragonyst Dust, you'll need to perform Uphyxes' Inverted Tower. However, to create Magenta Chalk, you'll also need some materials that you can only get through the Marid Crusher.]&f"]
	quest.3543563DF036D461.title: "&#AD00C8&a品红色粉笔&f&7[&#AD00C8Magenta Chalk]&f"
	quest.367E891A50991436.quest_desc: ["使用&c塞维拉的永久禁锢&r,我们可以结合几种不同的凋灵材料和下界合金,制造三份凋灵合金粉末.用这些,我们可以为自己制造最高级的基础粉笔,&a黑色粉笔&f.\\n&7[Using Sevira's Permanent Confinement, we can combine several different Wither materials and some Netherite to create three Witherite Dust. With these, we can create ourselves the highest form of Foundation Chalk, Black Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.367E891A50991436.title: "&a黑色粉笔&f&7[Black Chalk]&f"
	quest.38A1295878B68F83.quest_desc: [
		"不,不是那种.\\n&7[No, not that kind.]&f"
		""
		"&c阿弗里特恶魔&r是&c火焰&r的恶魔.它们是更高级的恶魔,其中一些是朋友,一些则……不是.这完全取决于仪式控制&c阿弗里特&r的强度.\\n&7[Afrit Demons are Demons of Fire. They are more advanced Demons, which some are friends and some are... not. It all depends on how strongly the ritual can control the Afrit. ]&f"
		""
		"因为我们还没有&a红色粉笔&f,我们只能召唤一个&9未束缚&r的恶魔,这意味着它无法被控制并且会具有攻击性.\\n&7[Because we don't have access to Red Chalk yet, all we can summon is an Unbound Demon, meaning it cannot be controlled and will be violent.]&f"
	]
	quest.38A1295878B68F83.quest_subtitle: "火热的恶魔!&7[Hot Demons!]&f"
	quest.38A1295878B68F83.title: "&6坎达尔的开放召唤&7[Kandar's Opened Conjure]&f"
	quest.39647A2473F6F7D7.quest_desc: [
		"我们的下一步是涉足&6灌注仪式&r.这些仪式用于将恶魔的魔法注入物品.\\n&7[Our next step is a foray into Infusion Rituals. These rituals are used to imbue items with the magic of demons.]&f"
		""
		"&6灌注仪式&r的第一等级是&e埃兹维乌斯的灵质强制&r.我们将使用这个仪式来制造你在这个模组中需要的几件物品.\\n&7[The first tier of Infusion Rituals is Eziveus' Spectral Compulsion. We'll be using this ritual to create several items that you'll need throughout this mod.]&f"
		""
		"建议在与你第一个仪式不同的区域创建这个仪式,因为三种主要仪式类型都是在前一个等级的基础上构建的.\\n&7[It is recommended to create this ritual in a separate area from your first one, because the three main types of rituals build off each previous tier.]&f"
	]
	quest.39647A2473F6F7D7.quest_subtitle: "给它撒点恶魔粉末™!&7[Put some Demon Dust™ on it!]&f"
	quest.39647A2473F6F7D7.title: "&e埃兹维乌斯的灵质强制&7[Eziveus' Spectral Compulsion]&f"
	quest.3D41D0092D94636B.quest_desc: [
		"如果我告诉你恶魔果实是可燃的呢？\\n&7[What if I told you that the Demon's Fruit is flammable?]&f"
		""
		"把我们的&c恶魔梦幻果实&r扔下去并点燃它,会产生&d灵火&r.这就是我们将一些主世界物品转化为&9异界&r材料的方法.\\n&7[Throwing our Demon's Dream Fruit down and setting it on fire will create Spiritfire. This is how we'll convert some overworld items into Otherworld materials.]&f"
		""
		"它也很漂亮.\\n&7[It's also pretty.]&f"
	]
	quest.3D41D0092D94636B.title: "&9异界&r的&a火焰&f&7[The Flames of The Otherworld]&f"
	quest.429B5A81DF6C43FE.quest_desc: [
		"&6阿布拉斯的开放命令召唤&r用于将&c阿弗里特&r恶魔引入猪体内.因为这个仪式没有使用&a红色粉笔&f,它的力量只够召唤一个&9未束缚&r的恶魔.\\n&7[Abras' Open Commanding Conjure is used to bring an Afrit demon into a Pig. Because this ritual is performed without the use of Red Chalk, it's only powerful enough to summon an unbound demon.]&f"
		""
		"具体来说,这个仪式会创造一个&c阿弗里特&r附身的&a僵尸猪灵&f,它会掉落一些恶魔肉,用于制作&a粉红色粉笔&f.\\n&7[In particular, this ritual will create an Afrit-possessed Zombified Piglin, which will drop some Demonic Meat, which is used to craft Pink Chalk]&f"
		""
		"&4警告:你可能需要多次进行此仪式以获得足够的恶魔肉.\\n&7[WARNING: YOU MAY HAVE TO DO THIS ONE MULTIPLE TIMES TO GET ENOUGH DEMONIC MEAT.]&f"
	]
	quest.429B5A81DF6C43FE.quest_subtitle: "多么……血肉模糊……&7[How... Fleshy...]&f"
	quest.429B5A81DF6C43FE.title: "&6奥杜斯的开放集会&7[Odus' Open Convocation]&f"
	quest.42F50CE7FE715583.quest_desc: [
		"要升级你的魔法存储能容纳的堆叠数量,你需要制造&d存储稳定器&r.\\n&7[To upgrade the amount of stacks your magical storage can hold, you'll need to make Storage Stabilizers.]&f"
		""
		"一旦制造完成,这些稳定器必须直接指向你的存储促动器的维度矩阵部分,而不是底座.它们最多可以距离5格远,但必须与矩阵有清晰的视线.\\n&7[Once made, these must point directly at the Dimensional Matrix part of your Storage Actuator, not the base. These can be up to 5 blocks away, but must have a clear line of sight to the Matrix.]&f"
		""
		"每当你想升级到更高级的稳定器时,破坏它不会摧毁里面的物品.但是,在它被替换或升级之前,你将无法向你的存储中添加更多物品.\\n&7[Whenever you want to upgrade to a higher tier Stabilizer, breaking it won't destroy the items inside. However, you will not be able to add any more items to your storage until it is either replaced or upgraded.]&f"
		""
		"下面是一个简单设置的例子!\\n&7[Below is an example of a simple setup!]&f"
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/occultism/storageupgradeexample.png width:200 height:150 align:1}"
	]
	quest.42F50CE7FE715583.title: "&a升级我们的魔法存储&7[Upgrading Our Magical Storage]&f"
	quest.47358ADC1470C82A.quest_desc: [
		"&c恶魔梦幻果实&r对你完全健康.但有一些副作用你应该知道.\\n&7[Demon's Dream Fruit is perfectly healthy for you. There might be some side effects you should know about.]&f"
		""
		"当你食用一个时,你有机会获得&3&a第三只眼&f&r的效果,让你能够窥视&9异界&r.世界中的某些物品可能并非它们看起来的样子,你需要这种”视野”来寻找某些用于进度的物品.\\n&7[When you consume one, you have a chance to get the effect of the Third Eye, allowing you to see into the The Otherworld. Certain items in the world might not be what they seem, and you'll need this \"vision\" to find certain items for progression.]&f"
		""
		"或者你可以点燃它,跳过寻找它们中的大多数.这取决于你.\\n&7[Or you can set it on fire and skip finding most of them. That's up to you.]&f"
	]
	quest.47358ADC1470C82A.quest_subtitle: "准备开始一段旅程&7[Get Ready for a Trip]&f"
	quest.47358ADC1470C82A.title: "&c恶魔果实&7[Demon Fruit]&f"
	quest.4C873491F6F0FFAF.quest_desc: [
		"使用&d灵火&r,我们可以将几种主世界材料转化为它们的异界变体.你也可以在&b&a第三只眼&f&r的效果下,通过冒险进入世界来找到几种异界材料.你可能会对你发现的东西感到惊讶.为了简化,有通过将它们扔进&d灵火&r来制造基本材料的合成配方.\\n&7[Using Spiritfire, we can convert several Overworld mats into their Otherworld variants. You can also find several Otherworld mats by going under the effects of the Third Eye and adventuring into the world. You might be surprised what you find. To make it easier, there are crafting recipes for the basic materials by throwing them into Spiritfire.]&f"
		""
		"&b安山岩&r转化为&3异界石&r,可用于点燃永久的&d灵火&r.\\n&7[Andesite converts to Otherstone, which can be used to light a permanent Spiritfire.]&f"
		""
		"&a&a橡树树苗&f&r转化为&9&a橡树树苗&f&r,但它们并不相同.当长成时,这些树看起来和普通的橡树一模一样.然而,在&b&a第三只眼&f&r的效果下,你将能够收获异界变体.\\n&7[Oak Saplings convert to Oak Saplings but they are not the same. When grown, these will look exactly like a regular Oak tree. However, under the effects of the Third Eye, you will be able to harvest the Otherworld variant.]&f"
		""
		"如果你收集原木有困难(即使有&b&a第三只眼&f&r它们也变成了普通的&a橡木原木&f),尝试从顶部收集它们.\\n&7[If you have trouble collecting the logs (if they turn into regular Oak Logs even with Third Eye), try collecting them from the top.]&f"
		""
		"&e钻石&r将变成&d灵调宝石&r,这些宝石将在我们后面需要的几个配方中使用.\\n&7[Diamonds will turn into Spirit Attuned Gems which are used in several recipes we'll need later on.]&f"
	]
	quest.4C873491F6F0FFAF.title: "&d灵火&r转化&7[Spiritfire Conversions]&f"
	quest.4CE571F942461909.quest_desc: [
		"&a仪式&f背包不错,但放置所有方块需要很长时间.既然你现在可以进行&c塞维拉的永久禁锢&r仪式,你可以制造工匠&a魔法仪式&f背包了!\\n&7[The Ritual Satchel is nice, but it takes a long time to place all the blocks. Now that you can perform the Sevira's Permanent Confinement ritual, you can create the Artisanal Ritual Satchel!]&f"
		""
		"&a工匠&f&a魔法仪式&f背包的功能与普通的&a魔法仪式&f背包几乎相同,除了它能瞬间放置仪式所需的所有物品,并且增加了右键点击&a金弓&f来擦除所有粉笔符文并收集所有其他物品(头颅、蜡烛和水晶)并将它们返回到背包的能力.\\n&7[The Artisanal Ritual Satchel functions nearly identically to the regular Ritual Satchel, except it instantly places all the necessary items for the ritual, and has the added ability to right-click on Golden Bowl to erase all the Chalk Runes and collect all the other items (Skulls, Candles, and Crystals) and return them to the Satchel.]&f"
		""
		"不,它不会恢复粉笔的耐久度.\\n&7[No, it doesn't restore the durability of the Chalk.]&f"
	]
	quest.4CE571F942461909.title: "行业工具:工匠&a魔法仪式&f背包&7[Tools of the Trade: Artisanal Ritual Satchel]&f"
	quest.4DF0D7B85065ADC9.quest_subtitle: "砍砍杀杀!&7[Hack and slash!]&f"
	quest.4DF0D7B85065ADC9.title: "行业工具:屠刀&7[Tools of the Trade: Butcher's Knife]&f"
	quest.4F35D04721DFC9FF.quest_desc: [
		"我们将要进行的第一个仪式类型是&9召唤仪式&r.这些仪式用于召唤不同类型的有用恶魔,以协助你进行粉碎、冶炼等,随着你达到更高级别的仪式.\\n&7[The first type of ritual we'll be performing is the Summoning Ritual. These rituals are used to summon different types of useful Demons to assist you in crushing, smelting, and more as you get to higher tiers of rituals.]&f"
		""
		"对于我们的第一个仪式,我们想召唤一个&a弗利奥特粉碎者&r恶魔.这个恶魔会为我们粉碎物品,这是我们制造一些更高级粉笔所需要的!\\n&7[For our first ritual, we want to summon a Foliot Crusher Demon. This Demon will crush items for us, which is something we'll need to make some of the higher level Chalks!]&f"
		""
		"首先,在工作台中把你的未绑定之书和你的&a&a魔灵全典&f&r结合.这会将一个恶魔绑定到书上,这就是我们仪式所需要的.\\n&7[To start with, combine your Unbound Book with your Dictionary of Spirits in a crafting grid. This will bind a Demon to the Book, which is what we'll need for the ritual.]&f"
		""
		"说到你的&a魔灵全典&f,是时候打开它了!在左侧,点击&d五芒星&r标签,然后点击&b阿维亚尔之环&r.你可能需要阅读一点来推进它.还有一种方法是点击\\”全部标记为已读\\n&7[Speaking about your Dictionary of Spirits, it's time to open it up! On the left, click on the Pentacles tab and click on Aviar's Circle. You might have to advance through it by reading a little bit. There is also a way to click \"Mark All As Read\" so it unlocks everything in the Book.]&f"
		""
		"This is what we're going to use to summon our new friend. On the right side, you can click the eye in the bottom-left corner of the image to build an outline of the ritual for you in the world. This is super helpful!"
		""
		"一旦你完成了多方块仪式,在中心&a献祭之碗&f水平半径8格内的任何地方放下4个(或更多,用于未来的仪式)&a献祭之碗&f,并在上面使用所需的物品.一旦你将你的绑定之书放入&a黄金献祭之碗&f,仪式就会开始!\\n&7[Once you've completed the multi-block ritual, place down 4 (or more for future rituals) Sacrificial Bowls anywhere within 8 block horizontal radius from the center Sacrificial Bowl and use the required items on them. Once you place your Bound Book in the Golden Sacrificial Bowl, the ritual will start!]&f"
		""
		"这就是仪式看起来的样子.\\n&7[This is what the ritual will look like.]&f"
		""
		""
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/occultism/aviarcirclenew.png width:200 height:200 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4F35D04721DFC9FF.quest_subtitle: "阿维亚尔之环&7[Aviar's Circle]&f"
	quest.4F35D04721DFC9FF.title: "&b我们的第一个&d仪式&7[Our First Ritual]&f"
	quest.5316DF321B45D2CA.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到&d&d神秘学&f&r!\\n\\n这个模组旨在通过征召&c&m恶魔&r &b灵体&r的帮助,以多种不同的方式帮助玩家!别担心,它们大多数是友好的.&o大多数&r.\\n\\n要开始,你需要获得一些&a恶魔梦幻种子&r.破坏一些草来获得它.\\n&7[Welcome to Occultism!\\n\\nThis mod aims to help the player in many different ways by enlisting the help of Demons Spirits! Don't worry, most of them are friendly. Most.\\n\\nTo get started, you'll need to get some Demon's Dream Seeds. Break some grass to get it.]&f"]
	quest.5316DF321B45D2CA.title: "&d梦见&c恶魔&7[Dreaming of Demons]&f"
	quest.53DEA3DFEDC4809E.quest_desc: [
		"别担心,这是阿布拉斯系列仪式的最后一个.它用于召唤&9玛瑞德&r恶魔,但即使它使用了&a红色粉笔&f,它的力量也不足以&9束缚&r这个恶魔.这意味着,不幸的是,你将不得不与它战斗.\\n&7[Don't worry, this is the last of the Abras series of rituals. It is used to summon a Marid demon, but even though it uses Red Chalk, it's not powerful enough to bind the Demon. This means that, unfortunately, you're going to have to fight it.]&f"
		""
		"这个仪式使用三叉戟作为祭品,这令人困惑,因为大多数祭品都是活物.所以,与其在完成的仪式圈上杀死一个生物,你只需将三叉戟扔向中心的碗来开始仪式.\\n&7[This ritual uses a Trident as a sacrifice, which is confusing because most sacrifices are living creatures. So instead of killing a mob on top of the completed ritual circle, you simply throw the Trident at the center bowl to start the ritual.]&f"
	]
	quest.53DEA3DFEDC4809E.quest_subtitle: "是鸟吗？是飞机吗？不,是一个未束缚的&9玛瑞德&r!&7[Is it a Bird? Is it a Plane? No, it's an unbound Marid!]&f"
	quest.53DEA3DFEDC4809E.title: "&4提比拉的吸引&7[Tibira's Attraction]&f"
	quest.54378277B8D28B1D.quest_desc: [
		"彩虹粉笔的”升级版\\n&7[An \"upgrade\" to the Rainbow Chalk, for those who don't like the rapid color-switching runes ruining their tediously crafted aesthetic. ]&f"
		""
		"功能与彩虹粉笔相同,只是所有符文都会显示为白色,并且现在也适用于基础粉笔.\\n&7[Has the same function as the Rainbow Chalk, except all the runes will show up as white, and it now works with Foundation Chalk too.]&f"
	]
	quest.56EC79AF11B0869E.quest_desc: ["&9泽奥夫伦斯恳求&r是&5附身仪式&r的最高等级.它只有两个用途:制造残忍精华,这是&a棕色粉笔&f的主要成分；以及制造艾瑟尼姆傀儡,它基本上就是一个&a铁傀儡&f,但永生不死且造成更多伤害.\\n&7[Xeovrenth Adjure is the maximum tier of Possession Rituals. It only has two uses: creating Cruelty Essence, the main ingredient in Brown Chalk, and creating an Iesnium Golem, which is basically just an Iron Golem that's immortal and does more damage.]&f"]
	quest.56EC79AF11B0869E.quest_subtitle: "最高级附身&7[Maximum Possession]&f"
	quest.56EC79AF11B0869E.title: "&9泽奥夫伦斯恳求&7[Xeovrenth Adjure]&f"
	quest.57282D7E31EE61EE.quest_desc: [
		"一旦你收集了一些&a粗&a艾瑟金属矿石&f&r,你可能想用前几个锭制造一把&d&a艾瑟金属镐&f&r.这不仅像&a灌注镐&f一样可以挖掘艾瑟尼姆,而且使用寿命也长得多.\\n&7[Once you've gathered a few Raw Iesnium Ores, you'll probably want to use the first few ingots to make an Iesnium Pickaxe. This not only mines Iesnium like the Infused Pickaxe, but lasts a lot longer too.]&f"
		""
		"给自己行个方便,做一个这个吧!\\n&7[Do yourself a favor and make one of these!]&f"
	]
	quest.57282D7E31EE61EE.title: "&a异界镐&r&7[The Otherworld Pickaxe]&f"
	quest.5831B3192C0E8C56.quest_desc: [
		"想远程访问你的存储？这可以通过&e&a稳定虫洞&f&r或&a&a存储访问器&f&r来实现.\\n&7[Want to access your storage remotely? This can be done with either the Stable Wormhole or the Storage Accessor.]&f"
		""
		"要使用&e&a稳定虫洞&f&r,请潜行右击一个&d存储促动器&r来链接它.然后你可以放置虫洞,使其充当另一个存储位置.\\n&7[To use the Stable Wormhole, shift-click a Storage Actuator to link it. You can then place the Wormhole to act as another storage location.]&f"
		""
		"&a&a存储访问器&f&r的链接方式相同,但它是一个无线遥控器,甚至可以跨维度工作!\\n&7[The Storage Accessor is linked in the same way, but acts as a wireless remote that can even work across dimensions!]&f"
	]
	quest.5831B3192C0E8C56.title: "&a远程访问&7[Remote Access]&f"
	quest.5ACE97EE75813006.quest_desc: [
		"这是关于&d仪式&r的主要信息来源.以下是基础知识:\\n&7[This is the main source of information on Rituals. Here's the basics:]&f"
		""
		"&l仪式等级&r:\\n&7[lTiers of Rituals:]&f"
		""
		"仪式(基本上)有四个等级,取决于你召唤的恶魔有多强大.第一级是&e小魔&r,然后是&a巨灵&r、&c火怪&r和&9巨魔&r.有些仪式属于中间等级,例如&6无束缚火怪&r等级.\\n&7[Rituals have (basically) four tiers based on how powerful the Demon that you're invoking is. The first tier is Foliot, then Dijini, Afrit, and Marid. Some rituals fall into in-between tiers, such as the Unbound Afrit tier.]&f"
		""
		"&l仪式类型&r:\\n&7[Tlypes of Rituals:]&f"
		""
		"主要有五种仪式类型,但我们在流程中只需要四种.主要的三种是&9召唤仪式&r、&5附身仪式&r和&6灌注仪式&r.每种仪式都会在它们首次出现在这些任务中时进行解释.第四种仪式是一种&d无恶魔&r&d仪式&r,意味着它使用了所有三种类型的零碎部分来执行特殊动作,而不直接使用恶魔.\\n&7[There are five main types of rituals, but we'll only need four for progression. The main three are Summoning Rituals, Possession Rituals, and Infusion Rituals. Each one will be explained the first time that they appear in these quests. The fourth type of ritual is a sort of Demon-less Ritual, meaning that it uses bits and pieces from all three types to preform a special action without the direct usage of a Demon.]&f"
		""
		"第五种类型,&e使魔仪式&r,在流程中不需要.但它们仍然可以召唤一些有用的朋友来帮助你!\\n&7[The fifth type, Familiar Rituals, are not needed for progression. But they can still be summon some useful friends to help you out!]&f"
		""
		"&l粉笔&r:\\n&7[lChalks:]&f"
		""
		"有两种类型的粉笔:基础粉笔和彩色粉笔.\\n&7[There are two types of Chalks: Foundation Chalks, and Colored Chalks.]&f"
		""
		"基础粉笔用于每一个仪式,每高一级颜色就深一个色度,从&a白色粉笔&f开始,到&a黑色粉笔&f结束.\\n&7[Foundation chalks are used in every single ritual, and each tier higher gets a shade darker, starting with White Chalk and ending with Black Chalk. ]&f"
		""
		"彩色粉笔是最常用的,但粉笔的颜色并不像基础粉笔那样直接与其力量相关.\\n&7[Colored Chalks are the most commonly used, but the color of the Chalk doesn't directly correlate to its power the same as Foundation Chalks.]&f"
	]
	quest.5ACE97EE75813006.title: "仪式基础&7[The Basics of Rituals]&f"
	quest.5AE80FF518B1BBA6.quest_desc: [
		"厌倦了随身携带粉笔、蜡烛、头颅和水晶吗？那就做一个&a魔法仪式&f挎包吧!\\n&7[Tired of lugging around Chalks, Candles, Skulls, and Crystals? Just make a Ritual Satchel!]&f"
		""
		"手持&a魔法仪式&f挎包时,通过潜行+右击,你可以用它装满绘制仪式圈所需的所有材料.\\n&7[By sneak + right-clicking with the Ritual Satchel in your hand, you can fill it with all the materials you need to draw a ritual circle.]&f"
		""
		"一旦你装好了挎包,只需右击任何预览方块即可开始(缓慢地)自动放置所选仪式的所有符文.\\n&7[Once you've loaded up the Satchel, simply right-click any preview block to begin (slowly) automatically placing all the runes for the selected ritual. ]&f"
		""
		"如果包里的任何一支粉笔耐久度低于40%,物品上的附魔光效就会消失,以提示你可能需要修理或更换一些粉笔了.\\n&7[If a piece of chalk inside the bag falls under 40% durability, the enchantment glint on this item will disappear to signal that it may be time to repair or replace some of your Chalks.]&f"
	]
	quest.5AE80FF518B1BBA6.quest_subtitle: "口袋仪式!&7[Pocket Ritual!]&f"
	quest.5AE80FF518B1BBA6.title: "行家工具:&a魔法仪式&f挎包&7[Tools of the Trade: Ritual Satchel]&f"
	quest.61999669BDE127F9.quest_desc: [
		"如果你还没注意到,一遍又一遍地制作和重做仪式对你的粉笔耐久度消耗非常大.\\n&7[If you haven't noticed already, making and re-making rituals over and over again is very taxing on the durability of your Chalks. ]&f"
		""
		"如果你担心粉笔会坏掉,但又不想为了制作一支新粉笔而重新进行整个仪式,那么这个仪式就是为你准备的!\\n&7[If you're worried about your Chalk breaking, but don't feel like doing the entire ritual to create a new chalk over again, then this ritual is for you!]&f"
		""
		"利用&a巨灵&r的力量,你可以将任何颜色的粉笔修复到最大耐久度!\\n&7[Using the power of a Dijinni, you can repair any color of Chalk to it's maximum!]&f"
		""
		"或者,你也可以使用像禁忌魔艺模组中的&a&a永恒陨星&f&r这样的东西来永久保存你的粉笔!\\n&7[Alternatively, you could use something like the 位阶l Stella from the Forbidden Arcanus mod to permanently preserve your Chalks!]&f"
	]
	quest.61999669BDE127F9.quest_subtitle: "你弄坏了,&m我们&r恶魔来修!&7[You break it, we Demons fix it!]&f"
	quest.61999669BDE127F9.title: "粉笔修复&7[Chalk Repair]&f"
	quest.6581D4AF1A6DE230.quest_desc: ["恶魔喜欢蜡烛.我想.\\n\\n为了召唤我们朋友的几乎每一个&a魔法仪式&f,你都需要一些蜡烛.你可以制作&a&a屠刀&f&r并杀死一些猪、牛、羊、马,甚至是商贩羊驼来获得一些&a动物脂肪&r来制作它们.事实上,你绝对应该去找商贩羊驼.我听说它们能做出很好的蜡烛.&m我绝对不是刚刚编的&r.\\n\\n否则,原版蜡烛也可以!\\n\\n&9&a魔灵同调水晶&f&r也用于几种仪式,所以不妨现在就做一些!\\n&7[Demons like Candles. I think.\\n\\nFor almost every Ritual to summon our friends, you'll need some Candles. You can create the Butcher Knife and kill some pigs, cows, sheep, horses, or even the Trader Llamas to get some Tallow to make them. Matter of fact, you should definitely find the Trader Llamas. I hear they make good candles. I totally didn't just make that up.\\n\\nOtherwise, Vanilla Candles can also work!\\n\\nSpirit Attuned Crystals are also used in several Rituals, so might as well make some now!]&f"]
	quest.6581D4AF1A6DE230.title: "仪式准备:&a蜡烛&7[Preparing for a Ritual: Candles]&f"
	quest.666EA8B8F13EB292.quest_desc: ["此物品用于捕捉生物以便运输或存储.它也是制作&6&aATM之星&f&r所必需的.\\n&7[This item is used to capture mobs for transport or storage. It's also needed for the ATM Star.]&f"]
	quest.666EA8B8F13EB292.title: "&d空灵魂宝石&7[Empty Soul Gem]&f"
	quest.67884BFA27870CCE.quest_desc: [
		"&d奥索林的无束缚召唤&r是&d无恶魔仪式&r的第二级.第一级对流程完全没用,它只用于复活使魔和将恼鬼变成悦灵.\\n&7[Osorin's Unbound Calling is the second tier of Demon-less rituals. The first tier isn't useful for progression at all, it's only used for reviving Familiars and turning Vexes into Allays. ]&f"
		""
		"这个仪式用于创造大量你可能无法(或很难)以其他方式获得的稀有方块、物品和材料.\\n&7[This ritual is used to create a ton of rare-ish blocks, items, and materials that you might not be able to (or it's hard to) get otherwise.]&f"
	]
	quest.67884BFA27870CCE.quest_subtitle: "为我们这些不那么喜欢试炼大厅的人准备&7[For the less trial-chamber-inclined of us]&f"
	quest.67884BFA27870CCE.title: "&d奥索林的无束缚召唤&7[Osorin's Unbound Calling]&f"
	quest.690B89D23134B624.quest_desc: [
		"拿起你的粉笔,绘制你的&d罗纳扎的接触&r仪式,准备创造终极粉笔*!\\n&7[Grab your chalks, draw your Ronaza's Contact ritual, and get ready to create the ULTIMATE CHALK*!]&f"
		""
		"你不再需要随身携带全套16支粉笔,你可以使用彩虹粉笔来绘制一个变色符文,它可以算作其中任何一支(除了基础粉笔,寻找虚空粉笔来把它们也加入组合)!\\n&7[Instead of having to lug around a full set of 16 chalks, you can use the Rainbow Chalk to paint a color-changing Rune that counts as any of them (except for Foundation Chalk, look for Void Chalk to add those to the mix)! ]&f"
	]
	quest.690B89D23134B624.title: "&z彩虹&r粉笔&7[zRainbow Chalk]&f"
	quest.6C1BBA559963B3DF.quest_desc: [
		"&a灵魂辞典&r是&d&d神秘学&f&r的&a指南书&f.如果你想继续这个模组,你绝对需要制作它!\\n&7[The Dictionary Of Spirits serves as the Guide Book for Occultism. You'll absolutely need to make this if you want to continue with the mod!]&f"
		""
		"&a辞典&f里面有一个任务风格的指南,如果你宁愿读它而不是做这些任务的话!\\n&7[The Dictionary has a quest-style guide inside of it if you'd rather read it instead of doing these quests!]&f"
		""
		"你还需要这本书来制作整合包中的几样东西,所以你差不多必须做它.:)\\n&7[You'll also need the book to craft several things in the pack, so you kind of have to make it. :)]&f"
	]
	quest.6C1BBA559963B3DF.title: "&c恶魔&r小书&7[Little Book o' Demons]&f"
	quest.6CC5FE34778F0DFA.quest_desc: [
		"玩这个整合包,你肯定会拥有太多物品.它就是这样运作的,如果你还没有解决存储问题,&d维度存储&r可能正适合你!\\n&7[You're bound to have too many items playing this modpack. It's just it works, and if you haven't figured out your storage situation yet, Dimensional Storage might just be right for you!]&f"
		""
		"要开始使用这个魔法存储解决方案,你需要制作&d&a维度存储促动器&f&r并将其放置在世界中.它的作用就像一个潜影盒,这意味着如果你打碎它,里面存储的物品不会丢失.\\n&7[To get started with this magical storage solution, you'll need to craft the Dimensional Storage Actuator and place it down into the world. This acts just like a Shulker Box, meaning if you break it, it won't lose any of the items stored inside.]&f"
		""
		"默认情况下,它有128个存储槽位,每个槽位最多可容纳16组物品,但带有&5NBT&r数据的物品除外.这些物品不会堆叠,并且会占用整个槽位,所以确保不要放那些物品!\\n&7[By default, this has 128 storage slots with each slot holding up to 16 stacks of an item, except for items with NBT data. These will not stack and will take up an entire slot, so make sure to leave those items out!]&f"
		""
		"如果你不确定哪些物品带有NBT数据,你可以随时查看存储任务线中的任务”NBT与你”以&a了解更多信息&f关于NBT!\\n&7[If you aren't sure what items have NBT data on them, you can always check out the quest \"NBT and You\" in the Storage questline for more info on NBT!]&f"
	]
	quest.6CC5FE34778F0DFA.title: "&c&m恶魔&r&d魔法存储&r!&7[Demonic Magical Storage!]&f"
	quest.6CCDEEDA2C99DA66.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r为AllTheMods整合包创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e保留所有权利&r许可下,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.6FEED25FFAC4101F.quest_desc: ["使用&a斯特里吉奥的高等束缚&r,你可以创造灰色糊状物.将其涂抹在一支&a含杂白色粉笔&f上以制作&a灰色粉笔&f.\\n&7[Using Strigeor's Higher Binding, you can create Gray Paste. Smear this on a piece of Impure White Chalk to create Gray Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.6FEED25FFAC4101F.title: "&8&a灰色粉笔&f&7[Gray Chalk]&f"
	quest.6FFFAE334DFAAAAB.quest_desc: [
		"你可能已经注意到,仪式往往……有点慢.但现在不会了!使用&c塞维拉的永久禁锢&r,你可以创造&b伊森尼姆&a魔法仪式&f碗&r.\\n&7[As you've probably noticed, rituals tend to be... a little slow. But not anymore! Using Sevira's Permanent Confinement, you can create the Iesnium Ritual Bowl. ]&f"
		""
		"当用它代替金制&a魔法仪式&f碗时,它会大大减少执行仪式所需的时间,降至原时间的四分之一!\\n&7[When using this in place of a Golden Ritual Bowl, it greatly reduces how long it takes to perform a ritual, taking it down to one fourth of its original time!]&f"
	]
	quest.6FFFAE334DFAAAAB.quest_subtitle: "超速仪式!&7[Super-speed Rituals!]&f"
	quest.6FFFAE334DFAAAAB.title: "伊森尼姆&a魔法仪式&f碗&7[Iesnium Ritual Bowl]&f"
	quest.74130EB1E4B8586D.quest_desc: ["使用&a伊哈甘的奴役&r,你可以牺牲一个悦灵、蝙蝠、蜜蜂或鹦鹉来召唤一只&6附身蜜蜂&r.击败一只后,它会掉落诅咒蜂蜜,这是制作&a橙色粉笔&f的主要成分!\\n&7[Using Ihagan's Enthrallment, you can sacrifice an Allay, Bat, Bee, or Parrot to summon a Possessed Bee. Upon defeating one, it will drop Cursed Honey, the main ingredient for making Orange Chalk!]&f"]
	quest.74130EB1E4B8586D.title: "&6&a橙色粉笔&f&7[Orange Chalk]&f"
	quest.78ECC28DD4BA9696.quest_desc: [
		"虽然你可以使用灵魂之火获得大部分&d异界&r材料,但你也可以使用&9&a探测杖&f&r来定位这些材料.\\n&7[While you can get most of the Otherworld materials using Spiritfire, you can also use Divination Rods to locate these materials.]&f"
		""
		"首先,你需要将法杖调谐到你正在寻找的材料.例如,如果你正在寻找&8异界石&r,你可以在&a安山岩&r上使用法杖来帮助定位世界中的异界石.\\n&7[First, you'll need to attune the Rod to the material you are looking for. For example, if you are on the hunt for Otherstone, you can use the Rod on Andesite to help locate the Otherstone in the world.]&f"
		""
		"一旦调谐到某种材料,你可以手持法杖并按住&a右击&f,粒子会朝着它调谐的最近材料方向射出.\\n&7[Once attuned to a material, you can hold right click with the Rod in hand, and a particle will shoot off in the direction of the nearest material it is attuned to.]&f"
		""
		"你仍然需要处于&3&a第三只眼&f&r的效果下才能采集异界方块.\\n&7[You will still need to be under the effects of the Third Eye to be able to harvest the Otherworld block.]&f"
	]
	quest.78ECC28DD4BA9696.quest_subtitle: "寻找&d异界&r材料&7[Hunting for Otherworld Materials]&f"
	quest.78ECC28DD4BA9696.title: "行家工具:&a探测杖&f&7[Tools of the Trade: Divination Rod]&f"
	quest.7B574DD5CC5ACAE3.quest_desc: ["在我们继续&d&d神秘学&f&r之前,是时候学习如何升级每种类型的五芒星了.每种五芒星都建立在前一种同类型的基础上.\\n\\n这意味着,你不需要为每个等级的&a魔法仪式&f(例如,分别为召唤&a巨灵&r和召唤&a小魔&r)建造单独的五芒星,你可以用一个五芒星处理多个等级的仪式.例如,&9法特玛的激励吸引&r建立在所有之前的召唤五芒星之上.\\n\\n因此,我建议为每种五芒星设置4个19x19的区域.一个用于召唤,一个用于灌注,一个用于附身,一个用于杂项仪式(野生和邪术).\\n&7[Before we proceed with Occultism, it's time we learn about upgrading each type of Pentacle. Each pentacle builds off of the previous of that type.\\n\\nThis means that rather than building separate Pentacles for each tier of Ritual (I.E. a separate pentacle for summoning Djinnis and for summoning Foliots), you can have one pentacle handle multiple tiers of Rituals. For example, Fatma's Incentivized Attraction builds off of all previous Summoning pentacles.\\n\\nBecause of this, I suggest setting up 4 19x19 areas for each Pentacle. One for Summoning, one for Infusion, one for Possession, one for the Miscellaneous rituals (Wild and Eldritch).]&f"]
	quest.7B574DD5CC5ACAE3.title: "五芒星前言&7[Foreword on Pentacles]&f"
	quest.7BCD4A425CF6199B.quest_desc: ["在击杀从&9泽奥夫伦斯召唤&r召唤出的慈悲山羊后,你会发现你多了一份残忍精华.将其与一些可可豆结合,制作&a棕色粉笔&f.\\n&7[After slaying the Goat of Mercy summoned from Xeovrenth Adjure, you'll find yourself one Cruelty Essence richer. Combine this with some Cocao Beans to create Brown Chalk.]&f"]
	quest.7BCD4A425CF6199B.title: "&#4E2C00&a棕色粉笔&f&7[&#4E2C00Brown Chalk]&f"
	quest.7F09F8F98C13F11B.quest_desc: [
		"没有&c献祭&r的恶魔&a魔法仪式&f算什么!:D\\n\\n大多数时候,恶魔只是喜欢物品,所以现在还不用太害怕.然而,如果你有一头最喜欢的牛,你可能需要担心了.抱歉了贝琪.\\n\\n&a&a献祭之碗&f&r用于放置仪式所需的物品.只要不覆盖任何必需的粉笔,它们可以放在仪式范围内的任何地方.\\n&7[What is a Demonic Ritual without a Sacrifice! :D\\n\\nMost of the time, Demons just like items so don't be too afraid yet. However, if you have a favorite Cow, you might need to be worried. Sorry Betsy.\\n\\nSacrificial Bowls are used to place items needed for Rituals. These can be placed anywhere within the Ritual, as long as it isn't convering up any of the required Chalk. ]&f"
		""
		"目前,你只需要四个,但以后每个仪式可能需要多达十个碗!\\n\\n&6金制&a魔法仪式&f碗&r用于放置在&a魔法仪式&f的中央来激活它,并且通常还需要一本束缚之书放在碗里.\\n&7[For now, you'll only need four, but later on you'll need upwards of ten bowls for each ritual!\\n\\nThe Golden Ritual Bowl is used in the middle of the Ritual to activate it, and also usually needs a Book of Binding for the Ritual in it.]&f"
	]
	quest.7F09F8F98C13F11B.title: "仪式准备:&6碗&7[Preparing for a Ritual: Bowls]&f"
	quest.7F59941D62E672B0.quest_desc: [
		"&d神秘学&f提供的不仅仅是帮你粉碎矿石的恶魔!\\n&7[Occultism provides more than just Demons to crush your ores!]&f"
		""
		"有恶魔可以为你移动物品、砍伐树木等等!!\\n&7[There are Demons that can move stuff for you, chop down wood, and more!!]&f"
		""
		"还有方法可以召唤被称为&d使魔&r的酷炫朋友,它们提供特殊增益,甚至为你战斗!一定要在你的指南书中查看&d使魔仪式&r!\\n&7[There are also ways to summon cool friends known as Familiars that give special buffs and even fight for you! Make sure to check out the Familiar Rituals in your guide book!]&f"
	]
	quest.7F59941D62E672B0.title: "&d使魔&7[Familiars]&f"
