	quest.6C31A50068FBA0EE.quest_subtitle: "灰色&7[Grey]&f"
	quest.6C31A50068FBA0EE.title: "&8&a美洲黑熊&f鸢尾&7[Black Bearded Iris]&f"
	quest.7264CC40170E461A.quest_desc: ["将罗马番茄与其第二阶段的牛排番茄结合,我们就能得到黑美人番茄.\\n\\n不过,它也有可能变成另外两种番茄.\\n&7[By combining the Roma Tomato with its second evolution the Beefsteak Tomato, we get the Black Beauty Tomato. \\n\\nIt does have a chance of being 2 other Tomatoes though.]&f"]
