	quest.4281BCDCE233F65B.quest_subtitle: "&a红色枫树&f + &a烟花火箭&f + 监守者卷须 + &a监守者刷怪蛋&f&7[Red Maple + Firework Rockets + Warden Tendril + Warden Spawn Egg]&f"
