	quest.4AFA3CB55F6C10C2.quest_subtitle: "露兜树 + 椰子&7[Pandanus + Coconut]&f"
	quest.4C3B7BAEA653587B.quest_desc: ["你可以用8个&9有瑕疵的&r或1个&c完&6美&e无&f瑕&d的&5太&4阳宝石&r来制作这些.\\n&7[You can make these with either 8 Flawed or 1 Perfect Solar Gem]&f"]
