	quest.6E9782258731E444.quest_subtitle: "白蚁木 + 幸运&7[White Ipe + Luck]&f"
	quest.6FBF112811FB707C.quest_subtitle: "白蜡树 + 白桦&7[Ash + Birch]&f"
	quest.708129CB530BAC67.quest_subtitle: "&a野樱桃&f + 可可&7[Wild Cherry + Cacao]&f"
	quest.70A4E2B0491634FA.quest_subtitle: "&a蔗糖苹果&f + 香蕉&7[Sugar Apple + Banana]&f"
	quest.70F7B018CD61E946.quest_subtitle: "&a深色橡木&f + 丛林&7[Dark Oak + Jungle]&f"
	quest.71AA40CB2948A8D7.quest_subtitle: "蓝悠 + 灵魂树&7[Blue Yonder + Soul Tree]&f"
	quest.73EA0CFA78C689F2.quest_desc: ["某些树苗通常在各种结构的战利品箱中找到.当然,作为一个空岛整合包,我们并没有那些结构.那么,我们如何获得那些树苗呢？背包？\\n\\n我有一个更好的答案,&a末影工作台&f.\\n\\n查看第3章中关于 &a末影工作台&f 的任务,了解更多 &a关于如何建造&f 和使用它的信息.\\n\\n等等,我是不是给错了交流发电机作为任务奖励……哎呀……\\n&7[Certain saplings are normally found in loot chests in various structures. Of course, being a skyblock pack, we don't really have those structures. So how do we get those saplings, then? Backpacks?\\n\\nI've got a better answer, the Ender Crafter.\\n\\nCheck out the Ender Crafter quest in Chapter 3 for more information on how to use it.\\n\\nWait did I give you the wrong Alternator as a quest reward...oops...]&f"]
	quest.74297A72584F5D7B.quest_subtitle: "桤木 + &a野樱桃&f&7[Alder + Wild Cherry]&f"
	quest.747BA0DB44A49A4F.quest_subtitle: "蛇果 + 沙梨&7[Red Delicious Apple + Sand Pear]&f"
	quest.74CD3FC35F245DF2.quest_subtitle: "蓝悠 + 闪烁阳光&7[Blue Yonder + Flickering Sun]&f"
	quest.75CE67D3AA75C798.quest_subtitle: "蛇果 + 澳洲青苹&7[Red Delicious Apple + Granny Smith Apple]&f"
	quest.762C54C261ED5D29.quest_subtitle: "柚木 + 桃花心木&7[Teak + Mahogany]&f"
	quest.768C07D1B5EB1FEB.quest_desc: ["这些可以在寒冷 &a海底废墟&f 内的可疑沙子和沙砾中找到.我们这里并没有寒冷的 &a海底废墟&f,所以只能靠阿拉卡基诺斯了.只需在他们家附近放一些沙砾和一些水源,他们就能工作了.\\n&7[These can be found in Suspicious Sand and Gravel inside Cold Ocean Ruins. We don't really have Cold Ocean Ruins here, so Alakarkinos will have to fill in. Just place some Gravel near their home, and some Source so they can work.]&f"]
	quest.768C07D1B5EB1FEB.quest_subtitle: "寒冷 &a海底废墟&f 可疑方块&7[Cold Ocean Ruin Sus Blocks]&f"
	quest.76A0592F4C294545.quest_desc: ["&a锯木机&f 将原木切割成锯末,并且比合成获得更多木板.锯末可以用来造纸.\\n\\n - 黄颜木原木还会给你黄颜木染料.\\n - 巴西苏木原木和染料木原木还会给你苏木精.\\n&7[The Sawmill cuts Logs into Sawdust and more Planks than you would get from crafting. Sawdust can be used to make Paper.\\n\\n - Fustic Logs will also give you Fustic.\\n - Brazilwood Logs and Logwood Logs will also give you Haematoxylin.]&f"]
	quest.76A0592F4C294545.quest_subtitle: "我也要木头&7[I Wood too]&f"
	quest.76A0592F4C294545.title: "锯木&7[Sawing]&f"
	quest.77D3546953550E39.quest_subtitle: "&a西黄松&f + 云杉&7[Bull Pine + Spruce]&f"
	quest.799CC9FEEDE471B1.quest_subtitle: "芒果 + 八角&7[Mango + Star Anise]&f"
	quest.7A3DD8CAD6A5692D.quest_subtitle: "蛇果 + &a糖枫&f&7[Red Delicious Apple + Sugar Maple]&f"
	quest.7B1693793419B769.quest_subtitle: "&a银橙&f + 樱桃&7[Silver Lime + Cherry]&f"
	quest.7B3920DE6306A94A.quest_subtitle: "柑橘 + 金桔&7[Mandarin + Kumquat]&f"
	quest.7D0AE6FCB0996218.quest_subtitle: "柚木 + 蚁木&7[Teak + Ipe]&f"
	quest.7D7DC3C695CD7236.quest_subtitle: "&a银橙&f + 云杉&7[Silver Lime + Spruce]&f"
	quest.7DA48EDCF28DBE03.quest_subtitle: "银杏 + 榛子&7[Ginkgo + Hazel]&f"
	quest.7E7637DAD2C242CB.quest_subtitle: "欧洲落叶松 + 云杉&7[European Larch + Spruce]&f"
	quest.7EC89242980768B3.quest_subtitle: "山核桃 + 野樱桃&7[Pecan + Wild Chery]&f"
	task.0E7EAD7D7DF5E7C3.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.3D3F0DB8237E5856.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6609E5E7EDE6F92B.title: "树苗&7[Saplings]&f"
	task.79889CC26DCD7F19.title: "自花授粉&7[Self Pollination]&f"
	quest.011F787E620DE9E8.quest_desc: ["要设置 &a封禁塔&f,你只需用 &a封禁塔&f 点击你永远不想再看到的生物.\\n\\n每个过滤器只能容纳1种生物,所以如果你不想让僵尸、骷髅、蜘蛛、苦力怕和末影人生成,你将需要5个 &a封禁塔&f.\\n\\n你可以通过简单地用它点击另一个生物来更换其中的生物.\\n&7[To set the Mob Filter you just have to click the Mob you never want to see again, with the Mob Filter. \\n\\nEach Filter can only hold 1 Mob so if you want Zombies, Skeletons, Spiders, Creepers, and Endermen to no longer spawn you'll need 5 Mob Filters. \\n\\nYou can exchange the Mob in it by simplying clicking a different Mob with it.]&f"]
	quest.011F787E620DE9E8.quest_subtitle: "他不请自来!&7[He's uninvited!]&f"
	quest.034A9FBCA6D79BB6.quest_desc: ["&a收割机&f 方尖碑需要一把锄头才能工作.\\n\\n(不会损坏的锄头可以永久使用,会损坏的锄头则需要更换).\\n&7[The Harvester Pylon needs a Hoe to work. \\n\\n(Hoes that can't break will work forever, Hoes that can will need to be replaced).]&f"]
	quest.09D18512037386C1.quest_desc: ["为了将 &a药水效果&f 注入,你需要填满一个药水过滤器.\\n\\n操作如下:让你自己拥有一个药水效果,然后 &a右击&f 药水过滤器 &a用于清除&f 你身上的效果并将其添加到过滤器中,重复此操作直到过滤器被填满并激活.\\n\\n这也适用于模组添加的 &a药水效果&f 或者你通常无法通过药水获得的效果,比如急迫或抗性提升.\\n&7[In order to put Potion Effects into you'll need to fill a Potion Filter. \\n\\nTo do so: have a Potion Effect on you, then right click with the Potion Filter to remove it from you and add it to the Filter, and repeat until it's filled and active. \\n\\nThis also works with modded Potion Effects or ones you can't usually get through Potions like Haste or Resistance.]&f"]
	quest.12ED1EE85E146A4B.quest_desc: [
		"收割机方尖碑作为一个非常简单的自动农场.将方尖碑放在水源上或水源中,它会自动收获并重新种植其设定区域内完全成熟的作物.\\n&7[Harvester Pylons work as a very simple Auto-Farm. Put the Pylon on or in the Water Source and it will automatically harvest and replant Crops that are fully grown in the set area around it. ]&f"
		""
		"区域可以设置为方尖碑周围3x3、5x5、7x7或9x9方块的范围.\\n&7[The area can be set to 3x3, 5x5, 7x7, or 9x9 Blocks around the Pylon. ]&f"
		""
		"它需要一把锄头来作用于植物,并且需要一个像箱子这样的容器放在它上方来存放作物.完成所有这些设置,如果它处于开启状态,它就会开始耕作!\\n&7[It will need a Hoe to use on the Plants and will need an Inventory like a chest above it to put the Crops. Do all that and if it's turned On it will start farming!]&f"
	]
	quest.18246A48C20B29D8.quest_desc: ["&a注魔&f 方尖碑的工作原理类似于信标,只是更好更便宜!\\n当药水效果通过药水过滤器放入后,无论你在哪里,它都会持续给你提供该药水效果!\\n\\n你没听错,灌注塔不再有设定的半径,现在无论你在哪里它都能影响到你.\\n&7[The Infusion Pylon works similar as a Beacon just much better and cheaper! \\nWhen a Potion Effect is put in by a Potion Filter, it will continuously give you the Potion Effect no matter where you are! \\n\\nYou heard me right, no longer is there a set radius for the Infusion Pylon, now it will reach you wherever.]&f"]
	quest.30B0240543253EFB.quest_desc: ["方尖碑是由我们自己的 &aMutant Gumdrop&r 制作的一个出色的模组!\\n\\n别让这个模组的体积让你低估了它!它提供了许多方尖碑,可用于多种用途,帮助让玩 Minecraft 变得更轻松.\\n\\n要开始使用,你需要一些 &a磨制黑石&f 来制作它们.\\n&7[Pylons is a wonderful mod made by our very own Mutant Gumdrop!\\n\\nDon't let the size of the mod make you underestimate it! It provides many Pylons which can be used for many things to help make playing Minecraft easier.\\n\\nTo get started you'll need some Polished Blackstone to make them.]&f"]
	quest.30B0240543253EFB.title: "&l方尖碑&7[lPylons]&f"
	quest.32E52AD6EF194A60.quest_desc: ["驱逐方尖碑的作用是让人们远离你的地盘.\\n\\n放置后,它会阻止任何未被列入白名单的玩家进入其周围设定数量的区块.\\n\\n&a区块&f 范围在其 GUI 的左上角设置,可以是1x1、3x3或5x5区块.\\n\\n另外,它不能设置得离出生点太近.我们知道你们这些捣蛋鬼想要什么,但我们不会给!\\n\\n要将玩家加入白名单,请查看玩家过滤器任务!\\n&7[The Expulsion Pylon works as a way of keeping people off your lawn. \\n\\nWhen placed down it will keep any Players who aren't whitelisted from a set amount of Chunks around it. \\n\\nThe Chunks are set in it's GUI in the top left from 1x1, 3x3, or 5x5 Chunks. \\n\\nAlso no it can't be set too close to Spawn. We know what you trolls want and we ain't giving it! \\n\\nTo Whitelist players check the Player Filter Quest!]&f"]
	quest.32E52AD6EF194A60.quest_subtitle: "滚出我的地盘!&7[Get off my lawn!]&f"
	quest.403F76908A8A5661.quest_desc: ["驱逐方尖碑会将玩家推出区域,但如果你希望 &l某些&r 玩家留在附近呢!那么你就需要一个玩家过滤器.\\n\\n用它 &a右击&f 一个玩家来将其设置进去,然后将其放入方尖碑中以将他们加入白名单!\\n\\n这样当其他所有人都被推出去时,你的朋友就不会!\\n\\n另外,默认情况下,方尖碑的所有者不会被驱逐.\\n&7[The Explusion Pylon pushes players out of the area, but what if you want lsome players nearby! Then you'll need a Player Filter. \\n\\nRight Click a Player with it to set them in it, and then put it into the Pylon to Whitelist them! \\n\\nSo when everyone else is pushed out, your friend won't be! \\n\\nAlso by default the Owner of the Pylon won't get expuled.]&f"]
	quest.5B5FC539BD1F4A73.quest_desc: [
		"这个方尖碑专门用于阻止 &a怪物生成&f.\\n&7[This Pylon is all about blocking Mob Spawns. ]&f"
		""
		"你可以使用 &a封禁塔&f 来仅阻止特定生物的生成,或者使用无生命过滤器来阻止所有生物的生成!\\n&7[You can use Mob Filters to block spawns of only certain Mobs or use the Lifeless Filter to block all Mob spawns! ]&f"
		""
		"你可以堆叠多个 &a封禁塔&f 来阻止更多生物的生成.此外,你可以更改工作区域以设定它阻止 &a怪物生成&f 的距离.\\n&7[You can stack multiple Mob Filters to block off more spawns. Plus you can change the Working Area for how far it blocks those Mob Spawns. ]&f"
		""
		"如果你使用无生命过滤器,它将忽略所有这些设置.\\n&7[If you use the Lifeless Filter it will ignore all those settings.]&f"
	]
	quest.5C2C29ECA67F9B49.quest_desc: [
		"有了无生命过滤器,你将永远不必担心25x25区块区域内任何生物的生成.\\n&7[With the Lifeless Filter you will never have to worry about any Mob spawns within a 25x25 Chunk area. ]&f"
		""
		"但这不包括强制生成,即来自刷怪笼甚至 &a刷怪蛋&f 生成的生物!\\n&7[This doesn't include Forced Spawns though, that is Mobs spawned from Spawners or even Spawn Eggs!]&f"
		""
		"25x25的范围将覆盖玩家附近所有生物生成的距离.敌对或被动.\\n&7[The 25x25 will cover every distance Mobs spawn near the player. Hostile or Passive. ]&f"
		""
		"这同样包括所有Y层级,方尖碑上方或下方,所以再也不用担心点亮洞穴了!\\n&7[This includes every Y Level as well, above or below the Pylon, so no more worrying about lighting up caves! ]&f"
		""
		"这个过滤器没有白名单功能,它会阻止所有生物的生成.\\n&7[There's no Whitelisting with this Filter, it will prevent every Mob Spawn.]&f"
	]
	quest.5C2C29ECA67F9B49.quest_subtitle: "终于清静了.&7[Finally peace and quiet. ]&f"
	quest.5E02AE661945306C.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 工作人员&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 撰写,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均在 &eAll Rights Reserved&r 许可下授权,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	task.35320BB07FB39D05.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.59DD89698DBAA215.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.616C07AFBAFA7AE4.title: "锄头&7[Hoes]&f"
	quest.008D186B4E0ED14F.quest_desc: [
		"&a蒸汽炉&f 是另一种使用蒸汽做有用事情的机器.\\n\\n通过将蒸汽输入 &a蒸汽炉&f,它可以作为其中任何物品的熔炉.将矿石熔炼成锭并烹饪食物.\\n\\n它是一个由 &a蒸汽炉&f 方块组成的2x2x2机器.\\n&7[The Steam Oven is another machine that uses Steam for something useful. \\n\\nBy putting Steam into the Steam Oven it will act as a furnace to any items in it. Making Ingots from Ores and cooking food items. \\n\\nIt's a 2x2x2 machine of Steam Oven blocks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_oven.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.008D186B4E0ED14F.title: "&a蒸汽炉&f&7[Steam Oven]&f"
	quest.020E6AF37A0421C8.quest_desc: [
		"&a水槽&f 就像外面有个桶.只是这个桶要大得多.它收集水并可以为 &a蒸汽机车&f 储水.\\n\\n产水量取决于生物群系和是否露天可见.\\n\\n它由3x3x3的 &a水槽&f 方块构成,中心是空心的.\\n&7[The Water Tank is like having a barrel outside. Just this barrel is much bigger. It collects water and can hold water for Steam Locomotives. \\n\\nThe amount of water is makes is dependent on the biome and visible to the sky. \\n\\nIt's made by a 3x3x3 Water Tank blocks with the center being hollow.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_tank.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.020E6AF37A0421C8.title: "&a水槽&f&7[Water Tank]&f"
	quest.032B654201E71618.quest_desc: ["这些&c轨道套件&r用于让你的&7矿车&r搭载实体(实体即生物).\\n\\n&c登车套件&r会拾取附近的任何生物并将其放入&7矿车&r.\\n&c下车套件&r将生物从&7矿车&r中卸载.\\n&c卸载套件&r会将&7矿车&r中的生物丢弃到其所在&6轨道&r的下方.\\n&7[These Track Kits are for using entities with your Carts (Entities aka Mobs). \\n\\nThe Embarking Kit will pick up any Mobs nearby and put them in a Cart. \\nThe Disembarking Kit unloads Mobs from the Carts. \\nThe Dumping Kit will drop the mobs in the Carts below the tracks its on.]&f"]
	quest.032B654201E71618.title: "用于移动实体的&c轨道套件&r&7[Track Kits for moving entities]&f"
	quest.035C52EF63AD23A7.quest_desc: ["因此,模组&l铁路工艺&r及其核心&5火车&r,都离不开&6轨道&r.\\n\\n&2原版&r轨道适用于许多情况,但得了吧,我们都知道它们很烂.&a增强型&f轨道需要一些更特殊的物品来合成!制作它们吧!(可能需要使用机器来制作这些物品,所以去看看任务的那部分!)\\n&7[Hence the name of the mod, lRailCraft, and what it revolves around, Trains, Rails are pretty important. \\n\\nThe Vanilla ones work for lots of these but come on we all know they suck. Upgraded ones will need some more special items for their recipes! Craft them! (They might require using machines to make the items so check out that part of the quest!)]&f"]
	quest.035C52EF63AD23A7.title: "&6&l轨道&r!&7[lRails!]&f"
	quest.068294A7C21DE550.quest_desc: ["&c轨道套件&r用于与&6轨道&r合成,以制作特殊的&6轨道&r.\\n\\n这些&6轨道&r对于&5火车&r相关的所有事情都很有帮助,例如:停止&5火车&r、移动&5火车&r以及发出红石信号.\\n&7[Track Kits are used to craft with rails to make special rails. \\n\\nThese rails will be helpful for everything Train wise like: stopping the Train, moving the Train, and emitting redstone.]&f"]
	quest.068294A7C21DE550.title: "&c&l轨道&r!&7[lTracks!]&f"
	quest.08457BEED799E600.quest_desc: ["这些新的&7矿车&r主要用于铺设&6轨道&r.\\n\\n&7铺轨车&r会放置&6轨道&r,而&7&a轨道拆除器&f&r会移除&6轨道&r.\\n\\n&7轨道更换车&r会用不同的&6轨道&r替换现有的,而&7轨道底切车&r会替换&6轨道&r下方的方块.\\n&7[These new Carts are mostly for laying down Tracks.\\n\\nThe Track Layer places down Tracks while the Track Remover removes Tracks.\\n\\nThe Track Relayer replaces the Tracks with different ones and the Track UnderCutter replaces the blocks beneath the Tracks.]&f"]
	quest.08457BEED799E600.title: "&7矿车&r与&6轨道&7[Carts and Tracks]&f"
	quest.0A43FD0B5C76C1C5.quest_desc: [
		"&l&7铁路工艺&r为我们添加了一个&a爆裂熔炉&f多方块结构,用于将铁转化为钢!\\n\\n建造它需要34个&a高炉砖&f.它的尺寸为宽3格、长3格、高4格.正中心的两格必须是空心的.当它完全成型并允许你访问其GUI时,你就知道它建好了.\\n\\n在那里,你可以放入任何形式的铁,来获得钢和粒状沙子.\\n&7[lRailCraft adds a Blast Furnace multiblock for us to transform Iron into Steel! \\n\\nTo build it you'll need 34 Blast Furnace Bricks. It'll be 3 blocks wide, 3 blocks long, and 4 blocks tall. The two blocks in the exact center need to be hollow. You'll know it's done when it forms all together and allows you to access its GUI. \\n\\nThere you can put Iron ,in any form, to get Steel and Granulated Sand.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_furnace.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0A43FD0B5C76C1C5.title: "爆裂(钢)熔炉&7[Blast (Steel) Furnace]&f"
	quest.104049993CC62E7F.quest_desc: ["高级物品装载器拥有普通装载器的所有功能,但可以在&6轨道&r附近的任何位置使用.旁边、上方、另一侧旁边都可以.使用&4撬棍&r来改变它的方向.\\n&7[The Advanced Item Loader is everything the regular one is but can be used from anywhere near the Track. Next to, above, next to on the other side. Use the Crowbar to change its direction.]&f"]
	quest.104049993CC62E7F.title: "高级物品装载器&7[Advanced Item Loader]&f"
	quest.1698565EBB68DC85.quest_desc: [
		"&6&aY型轨道&f&r是使用道钉锤制作的第二种轨道.它将两条&6轨道&r合并为一条.如果一条&6轨道&r与另一条相交,&6Y型轨道&f&r会将第一条&6轨道&r上的&7矿车&r移动到相交的轨道上.\\n&7[The Wye Track is the second track made by using a Spike Maul. It directs two Tracks into one. If you have one Track intersected by another the Wye will move Carts on the first Track into the intersecting one.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_wye.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.1698565EBB68DC85.title: "&6&aY型轨道&f&7[Wye Tracks]&f"
	quest.170118E3C3C072E5.quest_desc: [
		"&6道岔&r是道钉锤制作的最后一种&6轨道&r.它充当&6轨道&r的普通交叉口.&7矿车&r会保持原来的方向前进,但现在&6轨道&r可以相交了.如果两辆&7矿车&r在上面相撞会发生什么？它们会爆炸!!!我开玩笑的,但&e&a电力机车&f&r确实会爆炸.\\n&7[The Junction is the last Track made by the Spike Maul. It acts as a normal intersection for Tracks. Carts keep going the same way as before but now Tracks can intersect. What happens if 2 Carts hit each other on it? THEY EXPLODE!!! I'm kidding but Electric Locomotives will though.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_junction.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.170118E3C3C072E5.title: "&6&a交接轨道&f&7[Junction Tracks]&f"
	quest.175D943160C10646.quest_desc: [
		"&l&7铁路工艺&r使用许多机器来处理不同的事情,但主要是资源生产.\\n&7[lRailCraft uses many machines for different things but mostly resource creation.]&f"
		""
		"它们全都始于&a铁锭&f!\\n&7[All of them start with Iron Ingots!]&f"
	]
	quest.175D943160C10646.title: "&l&7机器&7[lMachines]&f"
	quest.17F7964611D893BE.quest_desc: ["&a流体装载器&f将有助于让你的&3&a蒸汽机车&f&r保持运行.它必须放置在&6轨道&r上方几格的位置,并将流体部署到&5机车&r或&7矿车&r中.\\n&7[The Fluid Loader will be helpful to keeping your Steam Locomotives up and running. It has to be placed a few blocks above the Tracks and it will deploy fluids into either the Locomotive or Carts.]&f"]
	quest.17F7964611D893BE.title: "&a流体装载器&f&7[Fluid Loader]&f"
	quest.184F98BE0F6710E2.quest_desc: ["这两种&c轨道套件&r用于配合&7矿车&r和红石使用.\\n\\n&c激活套件&r会激活任何经过其上的&7矿车&r.\\n&c探测套件&r会在&7矿车&r经过时激活红石信号.\\n\\n两者都类似于&2原版&r中用于普通&6轨道&r的对应物.\\n&7[These 2 Track Kits are for using Carts and Redstone.\\n\\nThe Activator Kit will activate whatever Cart goes over it. \\nThe Detector Kit will activate a redstone signal whenever a Cart passes over it. \\n\\nBoth are similar to their Vanilla counters for regular tracks.]&f"]
	quest.184F98BE0F6710E2.title: "用于红石的&c轨道套件&r&7[Track Kits for using Redstone]&f"
	quest.21693C4DE6531D73.quest_desc: [
		"&a磨粉机&f正如其名.它可以粉碎方块以获得合成材料,例如从砖楼梯获得砖,或从锭获得粉末.\\n\\n不过它需要能量才能工作!\\n\\n建造一个需要3x2x2的粉碎机方块.\\n&7[The Crusher is just as the name suggests. It can crush blocks to get the crafting materials, like bricks from a brick staircase, or dusts from ingots. \\n\\nIt needs power to work though! \\n\\nTo build one it's 3x2x2 of Crusher blocks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_crusher.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.21693C4DE6531D73.title: "粉碎机&7[Crusher]&f"
	quest.249E5C6893387E15.quest_desc: ["这些&c轨道&r专为停止&5机车&r和&7矿车&r而设计.\\n\\n&c锁定套件&r会停止&7矿车&r,并且只在收到红石脉冲时才会启动它们.\\n&c缓冲套件&r用于你的&6轨道&r末端,会停止矿车且不启动.\\n&c闸门套件&r会部署一个与&6轨道&r连接的&a栅栏门&f.\\n&7[These Tracks are made for stopping the Locomotives and Carts. \\n\\nThe Locking Kit stops Carts and only starts them when given a redstone pulse. \\nThe Buffer Kit is for the end of your tracks, will stop them and not start. \\nThe Gated Kit just deploys a Fence Gate connected with the track.]&f"]
	quest.249E5C6893387E15.title: "用于停止&7矿车&r的&c轨道套件&r&7[Track Kits for stopping Carts]&f"
	quest.283AB56F81EF03A5.quest_desc: ["为了给你的&6&a电力导轨&f&r和&e&a电力机车&f&r供能,你需要&e框架.框架&r需要被供能,并将能量传递到每个相连的&e框架&r.\\n&7[In order to power your Electric Rails and your Electric Locomotive you'll need Frames. Frames need to be powered and will move power to each connected to Frame.]&f"]
	quest.283AB56F81EF03A5.title: "&e框架&7[Frames]&f"
	quest.2869AB982799CF0C.quest_desc: ["&c&a单向通行&f轨道套件&r非常简单.&7矿车&r只能朝箭头所指的方向行驶.\\n&7[The One Way Track Kit is quite simple. Carts can only go where the arrow is facing.]&f"]
	quest.2869AB982799CF0C.title: "&c轨道套件&r &a单向通行&f&7[Track Kit One Way]&f"
	quest.2A30595DC6DDBFF7.quest_desc: [
		"&6&a电力轨道&f&r用于&e&a电力机车&f&r.它们需要由&e框架&r供能,是的,如果你碰到它,它会伤害你.\\n&7[The Electric Tracks are used for the Electric Locomotives. They'll need to be powered by Frames and yes it will hurt you if you touch it.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_electric_rail.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.2A30595DC6DDBFF7.title: "&6&a电力轨道&f&7[Electric Tracks]&f"
	quest.2AB0FA084739827A.quest_desc: ["要实际使用&9&a隧道盾构车&f&r,你需要一个&9&a隧道盾构车&f钻头&r.\\n\\n它们有4种不同的样式,挖掘效果取决于&9钻头&r的类型.\\n\\n它可以附魔并且有耐久度,所以你会想给它附魔!\\n&7[To actually use a Tunnel Bore you'll need a Tunnel Bore Head. \\n\\nThey come in 4 different styles and it mines dependent on the Bore Head. \\n\\nIt can be enchanted and has durability so you'll want to enchant it!]&f"]
	quest.2AB0FA084739827A.title: "&9&a隧道盾构车&f,钻头&7[Tunnel Bore, Bore Head]&f"
	quest.2D00F85379A4D591.quest_desc: ["物品装载器是铁路工艺中最基础的分配器.它必须位于&6轨道&r上方,并且可以配置为你想要装载到下方&7矿车&r中的物品.\\n&7[The Item Loader is the most basic dispenser from RailCraft. It has to be above the Track and can be configured to what you'll want loaded onto your Carts below.]&f"]
	quest.2D00F85379A4D591.title: "物品装载器&7[Item Loader]&f"
	quest.31094CC16E710040.quest_desc: ["&4撬棍&r是铁路工艺的主要工具.\\n\\n当对&5机车&r使用时,它会改变其朝向.\\n\\n当按住潜行键点击时,你可以连接&5机车&r和&7矿车&r.\\n\\n当直接对&7矿车&r使用时,会给它们一个轻微的推力.\\n\\n当对特殊轨道使用时,会改变它们的模式.\\n\\n不同的&4撬棍&r只是外观和伤害不同.\\n&7[The Crowbar is the main tool of RailCraft. \\n\\nWhen used on a Locomotive it will change the direction it's facing. \\n\\nWhen shift clicked you can connect Locomotives and Carts. \\n\\nWhen just used on Carts they give them a slight push. \\n\\nAnd when used on special tracks they change their mode. \\n\\nThe different Crowbars just give different looks and damage.]&f"]
	quest.31094CC16E710040.quest_subtitle: "”怎么,你要抢劫我吗？”&7[\"What, ya gonna rob me?\"]&f"
	quest.365D4B1DC953D406.quest_desc: ["&7矿车&r分配器会如其名所示.它可以将任何&7矿车&r分配到其前方的&6轨道&r上.需要红石信号来分配.\\n&7[The Cart Dispenser will do as the name suggests. It can dispense any Carts onto the Tracks in front of it. Needs a Redstone signal to dispense.]&f"]
	quest.365D4B1DC953D406.title: "&7矿车&r分配器&7[Cart Dispenser]&f"
	quest.38451B61E3FC075B.quest_desc: [
		"等等,我们又有了钢,这是否也意味着我们拿回了(煤)焦炭？是的!\\n要获得(煤)焦炭,你需要一个&a焦炉&f.要建造一个,你需要26个&a焦炉砖块&f,并以3x3x3的方式放置,中心留空一格.当你可以访问GUI并且它变成一个整体纹理时,你就知道它建好了.\\n\\n放入煤炭或煤炭块以获得(煤)焦炭和液体杂酚油!你总是可以放入任何原木来获得木炭和杂酚油.\\n&7[Wait we have Steel again does that also mean we get our (Coal) Coke back? Yes! \\nTo get (Coal) Coke you'll need a Coke Oven. To make one you'll need 26 Coke Oven Bricks and place them 3x3x3 with 1 block hollow in the center. You'll know it's done when you can access the GUI and it's all one texture. \\n\\nPlace Coal or Coal Blocks to get (Coal) Coke and Liquid Creosote! You can always put any log in to get Charcoal and Creasote.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_coke.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.38451B61E3FC075B.title: "&a焦炉&f&7[Coke Oven]&f"
	quest.3E75AFE3482834C5.quest_desc: ["&l铁路工艺&r是一个完全基于&5火车&r的模组!\\n\\n从&7矿车&r到&e&a电力机车&f&r再到&9&a隧道盾构车&f&r!它也有所有&5火车&r配件!&a交通信号灯&f、为&5火车&r提供动力的&a蒸汽锅炉&f,以及所有的自动化.\\n\\n为&5火车&r模型爱好者准备的模范模组!\\n&7[lRailCraft is an entire mod based off Trains! \\n\\nFrom Minecarts to Electric Locomotives to Tunnel Bores! It has everything Train accessory wise as well! Traffic Lights, Steam Boilers to power Trains, and automation for it all. \\n\\nThe model Mod for Model Train Lovers!]&f"]
	quest.3E75AFE3482834C5.title: "&7&l铁路工艺&7[lRailCraft]&f"
	quest.3E8C2E7769DFBF35.quest_desc: [
		"与&3&a蒸汽机车&f&r不同,你不需要在&e&a电力机车&f&r中放入任何东西.\\n\\n它依靠&6&a电力轨道&f&r下方&e框架&r提供的能量运行.\\n\\n是的,它只能在&6&a电力轨道&f&r上运行.\\n&7[Unlike the Steam Locomotive you won't need to put anything into the Electric Locomotive. \\n\\nIt runs off the power from the Frames beneath the Electric Tracks. \\n\\nYes, it can only be ran off Electric Tracks.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_electric.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.3E8C2E7769DFBF35.title: "&e&a电力机车&f&7[Electric Locomotive]&f"
	quest.4071BBBE12CACD2D.quest_desc: ["&5火车&r分配器是&7矿车&r分配器的升级版.它可以分配整个&5机车&r以及更多!设置你想要部署的模式,然后给它一个红石信号.\\n&7[The Train Dispenser is a better version of the Cart Dispenser. It can Dispense the whole Locomotive and more! Set a pattern for what you want to be deployed then give it a redstone signal.]&f"]
	quest.4071BBBE12CACD2D.title: "&a列车分车站&f&7[Train Dispenser]&f"
	quest.425E375A9EC127EB.quest_desc: [
		"&6&a强化轨道&f&r是普通&6轨道&r的升级版!它们速度稍快且不会爆炸.\\n&7[Reinforced Tracks are the upgraded version of normal rails! They're slighter faster and don't blow up.]&f"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"1\\n&7[1]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_reinforced1.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"2\\n&7[2]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_reinforced2.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"3\\n&7[3]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_reinforced3.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"4\\n&7[4]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_reinforced4.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.425E375A9EC127EB.title: "&6&a强化轨道&f&7[Reinforced Tracks]&f"
	quest.475E307844E3AF7F.quest_desc: [
		"蒸汽锅炉是&l&7铁路工艺&r中最有用的机器之一.它们需要一个燃料燃烧室和顶部的某种锅炉.燃料燃烧室可以是1x1、2x2或3x3.燃烧室的大小决定了顶部锅炉的最大尺寸.对于1x1燃烧室,只能有1x1锅炉.对于2x2燃烧室,可以是2x2x3锅炉.对于3x3燃烧室,可以是3x3x4锅炉.&a液体&f燃料将使用杂酚油加热.对于固体燃烧室,它将使用熔炉能使用的任何燃料.\\n&7[The Water Boilers are some of the most helpful machines from lRailCraft. They need a Fuel Firebox and some sort of boiler on top. The Fueled Firebox can be 1x1 2x2 or 3x3. The size of the Firebox changes how big the Boiler on top can be. For 1x1 Firebox it can only have 1x1 Boiler. For 2x2 Firebox it can be a 2x2x3 Boiler. For 3x3 Firebox it can be 3x3x4. The Liquid Fuel will take Creosote to heat up. For Solid Firebox it'll use anything a furnace can use.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_big_boiler.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.475E307844E3AF7F.title: "锅炉&7[Boilers]&f"
	quest.4A44623D8A307473.quest_desc: [
		"&6&a高速电力轨道&f&r类似于&6&a电力轨道&f&r,但更快!它们也需要普通&6&a高速轨道&f&r和&6&a电力轨道&f&r所需的东西.&c&a速度提升&f&r和为其供能的&e框架&r.现在你在拐角处和触碰它们时必须小心!\\n&7[The High Speed Electric Tracks are like the Electric Tracks but faster! They also require what the normal High Speed Tracks require and what the Electric Tracks require. Speed Boosts and Frames to power them. Now you have to be careful around corners and with touching them!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_electric_speed.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4A44623D8A307473.title: "&6&a高速电力轨道&f&7[High Speed Electric Tracks]&f"
	quest.50A286C268F38E09.quest_desc: ["在这个任务页面中,我花了很多时间为文本上色,试图帮助你这位玩家理解我指的是什么.&a仅用于&f让我意识到这可能更令人困惑,所以这里有一个图例!\\n\\n&5紫色&r代表任何火车或机车,包括电力和&a蒸汽机车&f以及连接的矿车.\\n&6金色&r代表任何轨道和铁轨,包括特殊铁轨,但不包括轨道套件.\\n&c浅红色&r代表任何轨道套件.\\n&4&a暗红色&f&r代表撬棍.\\n&3青色&r仅代表&a蒸汽机车&f.\\n&e黄色&r仅代表&a电力机车&f.\\n&9蓝色&r代表&a隧道盾构车&f.\\n&7灰色&r代表矿车和特殊矿车.\\n&7[With this Quest page I took a lot of time coloring the texts to try and help you the Player understand what I am referencing. Only for me to realize it might be even more confusing, so here's a Legend! \\n\\nPurple is any Train or Locomotive, so both Electric and Steam Locomotives and Carts attached. \\nGold is any Tracks and Rails, includes special Rails but not Track Kits. \\nLight Red stands for any Track Kits. \\nDark Red is for Crowbars. \\nCyan is for the Steam Locomotive only. \\nYellow is for only the Electric Locomotive. \\nBlue is for the Tunnel Bore. \\nGrey is for Minecarts and special Carts.]&f"]
	quest.50A286C268F38E09.title: "颜色图例&7[Color Legend]&f"
	quest.5128B119DFFF0C4C.quest_desc: [
		"&3&a蒸汽机车&f&r是最基础的&5机车&r.可以通过给它水、熔炉燃料并等待来为其提供动力.它需要持续的水来保持工作.\\n\\n别担心,那只是意味着从它顶部冒出的烟是&a水蒸气&f,对环境是安全的.嗯,煤炭部分对环境来说不是最好的……呃,这是&2我的世界&r,我们在乎什么!\\n&7[The Steam Locomotive is the most basic Locomotive. It can be powered by giving it water, furnance fuel, and waiting. It'll need constant water to keep working. \\n\\nDon't worry that just means the smoke coming out of the top of it is Water Vapor, which is safe for the Environment. Well the Coal part isn't the best for the Environment... eh its Minecraft what do we care!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_steam_locomotive.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5128B119DFFF0C4C.title: "&3&a蒸汽机车&f&7[Steam Locomotive]&f"
	quest.5180CDD196518F64.quest_desc: [
		"&6&a镀铁轨道&f&r,像&6&a废弃轨道&f&r一样,非常适合吝啬鬼.它们比其他&6轨道&r慢得多,但没有脱轨的风险!\\n&7[The Strap Iron Tracks, like the Abandoned Tracks, are perfect for the cheapskates. They go much slower than the other tracks but no risk of derailment!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_strap.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5180CDD196518F64.title: "&6&a镀铁轨道&f&7[Strap Iron Tracks]&f"
	quest.53594EBA9F7BA840.quest_desc: ["高级物品卸载器与普通版本类似,但可以从任何方向使用.除了方向之外没有区别.\\n&7[The Advanced Item Unloader is just like the normal part but can be used from any direction. Nothing different besides direction.]&f"]
	quest.53594EBA9F7BA840.title: "高级物品卸载器&7[Advanced Item Unloader]&f"
	quest.541D270451DA4320.quest_desc: ["&a转辙轨道&f将用于在不同特殊&6轨道&r之间切换车道.上面的&a箭头&f显示去向.\\n&7[The Switch Track will be needed for moving lanes between the different Special Tracks. The Arrows on it show which goes where.]&f"]
	quest.54F2CB52D3A7BA87.quest_desc: ["物品卸载器与物品装载器相反.它会从&7矿车&r中取出物品.这个也必须位于&6轨道&r上方.\\n&7[The Item Unloader is the opposite of the Item Loader. It will take items from the Carts. This one must also be above the Track.]&f"]
	quest.54F2CB52D3A7BA87.title: "物品卸载器&7[Item Unloader]&f"
	quest.55D7CD0FA8F1AE48.quest_desc: ["我们聚集于此的原因,&5火车&r.这个模组叫做&l&7铁路工艺&r,别表现得那么惊讶.\\n\\n有两种不同的主要&5火车&r和一种特殊的采矿&5火车&r.\\n\\n这些&5火车&r本身可能有点无聊,那么为什么不给它们挂上&7矿车&r呢!连接&7矿车&r与&7矿车&r以及&5火车&r被称为耦合,而断开连接则称为解耦.要耦合&5火车&r和&7矿车&r,请使用&4撬棍&r或带有耦合&c轨道套件&r的&6轨道&r.\\n&7[The reason we're all here, Trains. The mod is called lRailCraft don't act surprised. \\n\\nThere's 2 different main Trains and 1 special mining Train. \\n\\nThese Trains all by themselves can get a little boring, so why not attach Carts to them! Connecting Carts with Carts and with Trains is called Coupling, and to unconnect them is to Decouple. To Couple Trains and Carts use a Crowbar or a Track with the Coupling Track Kit.]&f"]
	quest.55D7CD0FA8F1AE48.title: "&7&l矿车&r与&5&l火车&r!&7[lCarts 'N' lTrains!]&f"
	quest.5820EDEF71340A1A.quest_desc: [
		"&6&a废弃轨道&f&r适合吝啬鬼和美观用途.它们可以用于在没有支撑的情况下跨越几个方块.它们只能在与行进方向相同的方块相距2格,或与相反方向方块相距1格的地方放置.不过它们有脱轨的风险,基本上你的&7矿车&r会被抛出&6轨道&r.\\n&7[Abandoned Tracks are good for the cheapskates and aesthetic. They can be used to bridge across a few blocks without support. They can only be 2 blocks away from blocks going the same direction, or one block from the opposite direction. They come at the risk of derailment though, basically your Cart will be thrown off the rails.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_abandoned.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5820EDEF71340A1A.title: "&6&a废弃轨道&f&7[Abandoned Tracks]&f"
	quest.5E750DB2244A67A1.quest_desc: [
		"&6转辙轨道&f&r是使用道钉锤敲击&6轨道&r得到的第一种.它可以帮助朝两个方向行驶,向前和向一侧.可以通过&6轨道&r旁边的转辙器来切换.\\n&7[The Turnout track is the first from hitting a track with a Spike Maul. It can help go two directions, forward and to a side. It can be switched with a Switch next to the track.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_turnout.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5E750DB2244A67A1.title: "&6转辙轨道&7[Turnout Tracks]&f"
	quest.5F458D79D43D8842.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&e保留所有权利&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.609CA1ACFA981BD5.quest_desc: ["&c路线套件&r与通行票一起使用.\\n&7[The Routing Kit is used with the passing tickets.]&f"]
	quest.609CA1ACFA981BD5.title: "&c轨道套件&r 路线&7[Track Kit Routing]&f"
	quest.61C93ABE07742DCD.quest_desc: [
		"&a蒸汽轮机&f使用蒸汽来产生FE和EU能量.\\n\\n它是一个3x2x2的仅由&a蒸汽涡轮机壳&f构成的建筑,里面需要一个涡轮马达,并通入蒸汽.\\n&7[The Steam Turbine uses Steam to make FE and EU energy. \\n\\nIt's 3x2x2 building of only Steam Turbine Housing, and it'll need a Turbine Motor in it, and Steam piped in.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_turbine.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.61C93ABE07742DCD.title: "&a蒸气轮机&f&7[Steam Turbine]&f"
	quest.64C105E1E2F97900.quest_desc: ["道钉锤用于普通&6轨道&r以&a切换&f它们的模式.对于尝试创建交叉口非常有帮助!\\n&7[The Spike Mauls are used on normal Tracks to switch their modes. Very helpful for trying to make intersections!]&f"]
	quest.64C105E1E2F97900.title: "”切换它们”&7['Switch em up']&f"
	quest.677C5D35DADA4A42.quest_desc: ["&c&a联结器&f&r用于连接或断开&7矿车&r.耦合是连接&7矿车&r的术语.\\n\\n它可以用&4撬棍&r配置为耦合、解耦或自动耦合.需要红石才能工作.\\n&7[The Coupler is for connecting or disconnecting Carts. Coupling is the phrase for connecting Carts. \\n\\nIt can be configured with a Crowbar to couple, decouple, or auto couple. Needs Redstone to work.]&f"]
	quest.677C5D35DADA4A42.title: "&c轨道套件&r 联结器&7[Track Kit Coupler]&f"
	quest.6C14D1B60124C2B2.quest_desc: [
		"&9&a隧道盾构车&f&r非常适合自动铺设&6轨道&r,尤其是在山体或丘陵下方.\\n\\n它需要3样东西才能开始工作:&9钻头&r、燃料(如煤炭)和&6轨道&r.一旦备齐这三样,就让它开工吧!\\n\\n记得留意放入其中的物品!\\n&7[The Tunnel Bore is perfect for automatically placing Rails especially under mountains or hills. \\n\\nIt'll need 3 things to start working: Bore Head, fuel like Coal, and Rails. Once it has all 3 just let it go! \\n\\nRemember to keep track of the items going in it!]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_tunnel.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.6C14D1B60124C2B2.title: "&9&a隧道盾构车&f&7[Tunnel Bore]&f"
	quest.6C163E005351FF6D.quest_desc: ["&c汽笛套件&r在红石激活时,会使&5机车&r鸣响汽笛.\\n&7[The Whistle Kit when active with Redstone will cause the Locomotives to set off their whistles.]&f"]
	quest.6C163E005351FF6D.title: "&c轨道套件&r 汽笛&7[Track Kit Whistle]&f"
	quest.6DB65926EE6D6C2E.quest_desc: ["这些&c轨道套件&r用于改变你的&7矿车&r的动量.\\n\\n&c变速套件&r会改变经过的&5机车&r的速度,需要红石供能.\\n&c助推套件&r在供能时会加速&7矿车&r,未供能时会减速&7矿车&r.\\n&c控制套件&r会给&7矿车&r一个小的推力,供能时会改变其推动方向.\\n&c节流套件&r会将经过的&5机车&r的速度改变为配置的速度,需要红石供能.\\n&c发射套件&r会真的把你的&7矿车&r扔出去!\\n&7[These Tracks Kits are for changing momentum with your Carts. \\n\\nThe Transition Kits change the speed of the passing Locomotive, needs redstone power. \\nThe Booster Kits will speed up the Cart if powered and slow down the Cart if not powered. \\nThe Control Kit gives the Carts a little push, when powered it'll change the direction it pushes it in. \\nThe Throttle Kit will change the speed of a passing Locomotive to whatever speed is configured, needs to be powered with redstone. \\nThe Launcher Kit will quite literally throw your Cart!]&f"]
	quest.6DB65926EE6D6C2E.title: "用于移动&7矿车&r的&c轨道套件&r&7[Track Kits for moving Carts]&f"
	quest.6E7C4228CD2B6BB9.quest_desc: ["这把&4撬棍&r有几种不同的模式,每种都会改变&5机车&r的外观.默认模式(在物品栏中悬停时描述)、无模式(变为&7灰色&r)、&6H&r&5a&r&6l&r&5l&r&6o&r&5w&r&6e&r&5e&r&6n&r模式(使其变得诡异)以及&cC&r&2h&r&c&r&2i&r&cs&r&2t&r&cm&r&2a&r&cs&r模式(使其变得喜庆)!\\n&7[This Crowbar has a few different modes, each with change the design of a Locomotive. From default which is described while hovering over the item in your inventory, none which goes to grey, Halloween which makes it spooky, and Christmas which makes it festive!]&f"]
	quest.75DD345164EE5CD9.quest_desc: [
		"&6&a高速轨道&f&r类似于&6&a强化轨道&f&r,但显然更快.不过它们需要&c轨道套件&r来帮助加速!并且在拐弯处要小心.\\n&7[High Speed Tracks are like Reinforced Tracks but obviously faster. They'll need Track Kits to help build up speed though! And careful around corners.]&f"
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/railcraft/rail_speed.png width:150 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.75DD345164EE5CD9.title: "&6&a高速轨道&f&7[High Speed Tracks]&f"
	quest.78D8F40AA9568511.quest_desc: ["&a辊压机&f是&a人力辊压机&f的改良版本.\\n\\n你无需一直盯着机器来合成物品,它会自动合成所有物品.\\n\\n唯一的问题是它需要能量!\\n&7[The Powered Rolling Machine is much better version of the Manual Rolling Machine. \\n\\nYou don't have to keep looking in the machine to craft things and it will automatically craft all of them. \\n\\nThe only problem is it needs power!]&f"]
	quest.7D40B80DBBC4E160.quest_desc: ["&a人力辊压机&f将成为你制作许多铁路工艺材料的小型合成机器!\\n\\n当你放入配方且可制作数量大于1时,即使你仍在查看它,它也会自动合成.当你在合成时离开&a金属辊压机&f界面,合成将中止,物品会放入你的物品栏.\\n\\n你必须手动制作最后一个配方!\\n&7[The Manual Rolling Machine will be your little crafting machine for many things material for railcraft! \\n\\nWhen you put the recipe in and it can make more than 1 it will autocraft while you're still looking at it. When you leave the Rolling Machine while crafting it will abort the crafting and put it in your inventory. \\n\\nYou must manually build the last recipe!]&f"]
	quest.7F187E291C3D5BA7.quest_desc: ["&a流体卸载器&f与&a流体装载器&f完全相反.它不是位于&6轨道&r上方,而是下方.它不是给&3&a蒸汽机车&f&r加水,而是取走它们的水.我不知道你为什么想这么做,但你可以!\\n&7[The Fluid Unloader is the exact opposite of the Fluid Loader. Instead of being over the Track its under. Instead of giving Steam Locomotives water it takes their water. I don't know why you'd want to do that but you can!]&f"]
	quest.7F187E291C3D5BA7.title: "&a流体卸载器&f&7[Fluid Unloader]&f"
	quest.7F4B734CFB0F0306.quest_desc: ["这些新的&7矿车&r类似于特殊的&2原版&r&7矿车&r.&7储罐矿车&r可以容纳并运输其中的任何液体.&7能量单元矿车&r则可以容纳并运输能量!\\n&7[These new Carts are similar to the special Vanilla Carts. The Minecart with a Tank will hold and move any Liquid held in it. The Minecart with an Energy cell will instead hold and move Energy!]&f"]
	quest.7F4B734CFB0F0306.title: "新型矿车&7[New Carts]&f"
	task.025A45B704969EAE.title: "&aY型轨道&f&7[Wye Tracks]&f"
	task.03AE084C781CBA31.title: "轨道套件&7[Track Kits]&f"
	task.11741300813AF742.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.15BD622D04888DD8.title: "矿车&7[Carts]&f"
	task.19E2DE9D89B89D7B.title: "尖刺大锤&7[Spike Mauls]&f"
	task.1E77B21EA9F2E9A7.title: "燃料燃烧室&7[Fueled Fireboxes]&f"
	task.2606DDF2AE263B42.title: "轨道套件&7[Track Kits]&f"
	task.2A2D77813F3127A6.title: "轨道&7[Rails]&f"
	task.3490AE43AD653256.title: "道岔轨道&7[Turnout Tracks]&f"
	task.382933BEE2BCBD64.title: "&a隧道盾构车&f Heads&7[Tunnel Bore Heads]&f"
	task.395D321BFFDB098A.title: "&a交接轨道&f&7[Junction Tracks]&f"
	task.3E8F4263F7053EDD.title: "矿车&7[Carts]&f"
	task.653ED58A9B65C796.title: "撬棍&7[Crowbars]&f"
	task.6A4FADC04E1C9DA7.title: "&a蒸汽锅炉&f储罐&7[Steam Boiler Tanks]&f"
	task.6C12449632AD53DC.title: "轨道套件&7[Track Kits]&f"
	task.6D074E91F5BFC2A8.title: "轨道套件&7[Track Kits]&f"
	task.7B128D5D8D5530A8.title: "染色&7[Coloring]&f"
	task.7BB13793B38DFC2C.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.002D65E4D7E8F62B.title: "二级分级器催化剂&7[Tier 2 Grader Catalyst]&f"
	quest.036D5767E07005BC.quest_desc: ["&b排放口&r是我们用来提取&7液态金属&r的部件.是的,不幸的是,它对我们徒手或桶来说都太烫了.\\n\\n将&c&l冶炼炉&r&7龙头&r连接到&b排放口&r,通过&a右击&f龙头来排出&7液态金属&r.\\n\\n你还可以在查看&b排放口&r时,查看&c&l冶炼炉&r内的液体量!\\n&7[Drains are what we'll use to extract our the Liquid Metals. Yes, it is unfortunately too hot for our Hands or Buckets. \\n\\nConnect the lFoundry Tap to the Drain, to drain out the Liquid Metals when Right Clicking the Tap. \\n\\nYou can also view the amounts of Liquids in the lFoundry when viewing the Drain!]&f"]
	quest.036D5767E07005BC.title: "&c&l冶炼炉&r&b排放口&7[lFoundry Drains]&f"
	quest.047F3F99035CE623.quest_subtitle: "我渴望矿井&7[I yearn for the Mines]&f"
	quest.061A51A0EC13CA0F.quest_desc: ["现在我们有了&a控制器&r、&b排放口&r和&4储罐&r,我们还需要几个方块.\\n\\n首先是&6液体加热线圈&r.这些将构成&c&l冶炼炉&r的地板,并且是加热&c&l冶炼炉&r所必需的.\\n\\n最后是&c&l冶炼炉&r窗户或&c&a火焰砖&f&r.这些我们将用于建造结构的其余部分!字面意义上的建筑方块.\\n\\n&c&l冶炼炉&r不需要建造外框,所以每个角落都可以是空的；但它必须有4面墙和一个地板才能完成.如果有缺失的方块,&a控制器&r会告诉你位置.\\n\\n&c&l冶炼炉&r的内部可以小到1x1,只要它有&a控制器&r、&6液体加热线圈&r,并且其他墙面填满!\\n\\n不过我不建议造这么小的,因为&c&l冶炼炉&r越大,内部空间就越多!\\n\\n当&a控制器&r像熔炉一样亮起,并且&6液体加热线圈&r变成&6橙色&r时,你就知道&c&l冶炼炉&r建好了.\\n&7[Now that we have a Controller, Drains, and Tanks, we'll need a few more Blocks. \\n\\nFirst, is Liquid Heating Coils. These will make up the floor of the lFoundry, and are needed to Heat up the lFoundry. \\n\\nLast is either lFoundry Windows or Fire Bricks. These are what we'll use for the rest of the structure! The building blocks, quite literally. \\n\\nThe lFoundry will not need the frame built out, so every corner can remain empty; but it must have 4 Walls and a Floor to be completed. The Controller will tell you where a Block is missing, if there is one. \\n\\nThe lFoundry can be as small as 1x1 on the inside, as long as it has a Controller, Liquid Heating Coils, and the other Walls filled! \\n\\nI don't recommend making one so small though, as the bigger the lFoundry, the more space it has in it! \\n\\nYou'll know the lFoundry is built, when the Controller lights up like a Furnace, and the Liquid Heating Coils turn Orange.]&f"]
	quest.061A51A0EC13CA0F.title: "建造&c&l冶炼炉&r&7[Building the lFoundry]&f"
	quest.083ABBA1C45FF960.quest_subtitle: "只是一个&a割草器&f&7[Just a Lawn Mower]&f"
	quest.0947B4ED95B0267E.quest_desc: ["为物品和工具镀层.\\n\\n下界合金是一种极好的镀层材料.\\n&7[Coats an items and tools.\\n\\nNetherite makes a great coating material.]&f"]
	quest.0947B4ED95B0267E.quest_subtitle: "绝对不只是为了下界合金&7[Totally not just for Netherite]&f"
	quest.0D26E5EF6CFCFDBF.quest_desc: ["比匕首更高的耐久度,但伤害和速度较低.\\n&7[Higher Durability than a Dagger, but lower damage and speed.]&f"]
	quest.0D26E5EF6CFCFDBF.quest_subtitle: "刺刺刺&7[Stabby]&f"
	quest.0DF4B01CC5B49E4E.quest_desc: ["使用这个铸模,你可以制作基础剑!可靠的伤害和可靠的速度.\\n&7[With this Cast, you can make the basic sword! Reliable damage and reliable speed.]&f"]
	quest.0DF4B01CC5B49E4E.quest_subtitle: "可靠的老伙计&7[Good ol' Reliable]&f"
	quest.0EF9F10A2178451F.quest_desc: ["&c&l冶炼炉&r的所有部件(除了龙头、&a浇铸台&f和铸盆)都可以染成任何&z颜色&r.&z颜色&r在&c&l冶炼炉&r中也是可以互换的,所以如果你喜欢,可以拥有多色的&c&l冶炼炉&r.\\n&7[All parts of the lFoundry (except Taps, Casting Tables, and Basins) can be dyed to any zColor. zColors are interchangeable in a lFoundry, too, so you can have multi-colored lFoundries, if you like.]&f"]
	quest.0EF9F10A2178451F.title: "&z可染色&r的&c&l冶炼炉&r&z部件&r&7[zDyeable lFoundry zParts]&f"
	quest.0FEAD3CA2CC4A8B1.title: "三级星光充能器催化剂&7[Tier 3 Starlight Charger Catalyst]&f"
	quest.11B0B93D725ABE43.quest_desc: ["&d寂静装备&f可以使用&9&a修理工具包&f&r修复.\\n\\n要修复物品,将&a修理工具包&f放入合成网格,然后放入修复工具所需的材料.这将”填充”&a修理工具包&f.\\n\\n要修复工具,在合成网格中将填充好的&a修理工具包&f与你想要修复的工具结合.\\n&7[Silent Gear gear can be repaired using a Repair Kit.\\n\\nTo repair an item, place the Repair Kit into a crafting grid, then place the materials needed to repair the tool in with it. This will \"fill\" the Repair Kit.\\n\\nTo repair the tool, combine the filled Repair Kit with the tool you'd like to repair in a crafting grid.]&f"]
	quest.11B0B93D725ABE43.quest_subtitle: "无需铁砧&7[No Anvils required]&f"
	quest.158B24939A269D83.quest_desc: ["尖端升级用于提高工具的挖掘等级.\\n\\n例如:如果你有一把&a铁镐&f和1颗钻石,你可以制作一个钻石尖端升级,并将其放在你的镐上.这将允许它挖掘黑曜石,并给予属性提升.\\n&7[The Tip Upgrade is used to increase the mining level of a tool.\\n\\nFor example: If you have an Iron Pickaxe, with 1 Diamond, you can make a Diamond Tip Upgrade, and place it on your pickaxe. This will allow it to mine Obsidian, as well as give it a stat boost.]&f"]
	quest.158B24939A269D83.quest_subtitle: "当你找不到3颗钻石时&7[For when you don't find 3 Diamonds]&f"
	quest.2156C00E30424844.quest_desc: ["&4储罐&r用于向我们的&c&l冶炼炉&r添加液体.\\n\\n主要是燃料.\\n\\n主要是&c熔岩&r!\\n\\n这似乎是实际为&c&l冶炼炉&r供能的唯一方法之一.\\n&7[Tanks are made for adding Liquids into our lFoundry. \\n\\nMostly Fuel. \\n\\nMostly Lava! \\n\\nThat appears to be one of the only ways to actually Fuel the lFoundry.]&f"]
	quest.2156C00E30424844.title: "&l&c冶炼炉&r&4储罐&7[lFoundry Tanks]&f"
	quest.222D08F43B995FED.quest_subtitle: "试试看能不能砸出凹痕&7[Try and dent this]&f"
	quest.22A0A9C81A5C85A1.quest_subtitle: "将所有东西固定在一起&7[Holding everything together]&f"
	quest.262036FE8E87F50A.quest_subtitle: "&a3x3挖掘&f&7[3x3 Mining]&f"
	quest.26F9DB31A835B69C.quest_desc: ["&n冶炼炉&r:&a就绪&r\\n&n冶炼炉中的液态金属&r:&a就绪&r\\n\\n现在我们怎么把它弄出来？\\n\\n还记得我们之前的朋友吗？那个&c&l冶炼炉&r&b排放口&r？我们需要让它认识我们的新朋友,&c&l冶炼炉&r&7龙头&r.\\n\\n将&c&l冶炼炉&r&7龙头&r放在&b排放口&r上,现在我们可以在它下面放置方块来将&7液态金属&r排入……\\n\\n像&8铸盆&r这样的方块,它可以将大约900mB的&7液态金属&r变成完整的&7金属块&r.\\n\\n或者&8&a浇铸台&f&r,这是我们需要用来制作……\\n&7[Foundry: Check \\nLiquid Metal in Foundry: Check \\n\\nNow how do we get it out? \\n\\nRemember our friend from earlier? The lFoundry Drain? We'll need to acquaint him with our new friend, the lFoundry Tap. \\n\\nPlace the lFoundry Tap on the Drain, now we can place Blocks beneath it to drain the Liquid Metal into... \\n\\nBlocks like the Casting Bin, which will turn about 900mB of Liquid Metal, into the full Metal Block. \\n\\nOr the Casting Table which is what we'll need in order to make...]&f"]
	quest.26F9DB31A835B69C.title: "浇铸物品&7[Casting Items]&f"
	quest.29131C3532610ADF.quest_desc: ["这是一个用于星光充能器的二级支柱顶盖.\\n&7[This is a Tier 2 Pillar Cap for the Starlight Charger.]&f"]
	quest.29131C3532610ADF.title: "二级星光充能器支柱顶盖&7[Tier 2 Starlight Charger Pillar Cap]&f"
	quest.2BF119DD5D977409.title: "二级星光充能器催化剂&7[Tier 2 Starlight Charger Catalyst]&f"
	quest.2EB96FF06627FD9A.quest_desc: ["&a拆解回收机&f允许你将装备分解成其组成的物品.\\n\\n例如:如果你放入一些&a钻石靴子&f,你将得到4颗钻石.\\n&7[The Salvager allows you to break down gear into the items they from.\\n\\nFor example: If you put in some Diamond Boots you will get 4 Diamonds back.]&f"]
	quest.2EB96FF06627FD9A.quest_subtitle: "分解(某些)物品!&7[Breaking down (some) items!]&f"
	quest.2EB96FF06627FD9A.title: "回收机&7[Salvager]&f"
	quest.3722B43822F80470.quest_desc: ["比剑更高的伤害,但速度更慢.\\n&7[More damage than a Sword, but slower.]&f"]
	quest.3722B43822F80470.quest_subtitle: "释放你内心的武士&7[Release Your Inner Samurai]&f"
	quest.3930404D5C8B44EB.quest_desc: ["这用于创建自定义合金.\\n\\n它也是获得&a提尔钢&f的唯一方法!\\n&7[This is used to create custom alloys.\\n\\nIt is also the only way to get Tyrian Steel!]&f"]
	quest.3930404D5C8B44EB.quest_subtitle: "组合材料&7[Combines Materials]&f"
	quest.39B85DB54B1037FE.quest_desc: ["比剑稍快,但伤害较低.\\n&7[Slightly faster than a Sword, but lower damage.]&f"]
	quest.39B85DB54B1037FE.quest_subtitle: "厚剑&7[Thicc Sword]&f"
	quest.3AC03D1FA5C341A7.quest_desc: ["&a再结晶器&f允许你将不同的晶体组合在一起,制作新的晶体,用于制造武器、工具和盔甲.\\n&7[The Recrystallizer allows you to combine together different crystals to make new crystals to use to make weapons, tools and armor.]&f"]
	quest.3B560B2ECE331CAF.quest_desc: ["这是一个用于星光充能器的三级支柱顶盖.\\n&7[This is a Tier 3 Pillar Cap for the Starlight Charger.]&f"]
	quest.3B560B2ECE331CAF.title: "三级星光充能器支柱顶盖&7[Tier 3 Starlight Charger Pillar Cap]&f"
	quest.3D2C6FF462B17205.quest_desc: ["低伤害,极高的&a攻击速度&f.减少目标的无敌时间.\\n&7[Low damage, very high attack speed. Reduces the invincibility time of the target.]&f"]
	quest.3D2C6FF462B17205.quest_subtitle: "刺刺刺&7[Stabby Stab]&f"
	quest.3F39BEB788175CEF.quest_subtitle: "3x3挖掘!&7[3x3 Digging!]&f"
	quest.405DCD3E36232EEA.quest_desc: ["比剑伤害低,但攻击距离更长.\\n&7[Less damage than a Sword, but longer reach.]&f"]
	quest.405DCD3E36232EEA.quest_subtitle: "释放你内心的斯巴达人&7[Release Your Inner Spartan]&f"
	quest.427516AA3E8C9442.quest_subtitle: "多功能锄&7[Versatile Hoe]&f"
	quest.45899579D9B92D91.quest_desc: ["&a控制器&r是&c&l冶炼炉&r的核心.\\n\\n每个&c&l冶炼炉&r至少需要1个才能建成.\\n\\n我们可以使用&c&l冶炼炉&r来查看&c&l冶炼炉&r的GUI.在这里我们可以看到&c&l冶炼炉&r内的液体量.\\n\\n我们还可以用它来放入和取出&c&l冶炼炉&r中的物品.\\n&7[The Controller is the heart of the lFoundry. \\n\\nEach lFoundry will need atleast 1, to be made. \\n\\nWe can use the lFoundry to view the GUI of the lFoundry. Here we can see the amounts of Liquids within the lFoundry. \\n\\nWe can also use it to put and take Items in and out of the lFoundry.]&f"]
	quest.45899579D9B92D91.title: "&c&l冶炼炉&r&a控制器&7[lFoundry Controller]&f"
	quest.462C1F75A2FB9F02.quest_subtitle: "威利在哪？&7[Where's Willy?]&f"
	quest.48D358470A019E7A.title: "一级星光充能器催化剂&7[Tier 1 Starlight Charger Catalyst]&f"
	quest.52CDB46F6CBF007B.quest_subtitle: "你喜欢这个吗？&7[Are you digging this?]&f"
	quest.63CAD77A4488F2CE.quest_subtitle: "镐 + 斧 + 锹&7[Pickaxe + Axe + Shovel]&f"
	quest.657B3116A6419420.quest_subtitle: "你自己的手柄!&7[Your own Handle!]&f"
	quest.67216EC5274F08B9.quest_subtitle: "剪羊毛高手专用&7[Used by Shear-perds]&f"
	quest.69383DA579901E7E.quest_subtitle: "让我问你这个问题&7[Let me Axe you this]&f"
	quest.6A393C7A24899E3E.quest_desc: ["将锭放入分级器并配合分级器催化剂,可以赋予材料一个等级.\\n\\n等级越好,材料的属性就越好.\\n\\n最好的等级是”MAX”.\\n&7[Placing an ingot in the Grader with a Grader Catalyst will give the material a grade.\\n\\nThe better the grade, the better the stats are on the material.\\n\\nThe best grade is \"MAX\".]&f"]
	quest.6A393C7A24899E3E.quest_subtitle: "&a材料&f测试仪&7[The Material Tester]&f"
	quest.6B78378BC8036227.title: "一级分级器催化剂&7[Tier 1 Grader Catalyst]&f"
	quest.6BBC440BD0AD0E93.quest_desc: ["有些人喜欢&9&l&d寂静装备&f&r,有些人喜欢&7&l匠魂&r.\\n\\n我们决定不二选一,而是通过使用&9&l&d寂静装备&f&r和&c&l高效金属加工&r来兼收并蓄!\\n\\n&c&l高效金属加工&r将改变我们获取&9&l寂静&r物品的方式.现在我们将不再使用&9蓝图&r,而是需要&8铸模&r和一个&c&l冶炼炉&r.\\n\\n要开始制作&c&l冶炼炉&r,先从&c&a耐火黏土块&f&r开始.\\n&7[Some people like lSilent Gear, while some like lTinker's Construct. \\n\\nInstead of choosing between them, we've decided to take the best of both worlds by using lSilent Gear and lProductive Metalworks! \\n\\nlProductive Metalworks will change how we obtain our lSilent Items. Instead of using Blueprints, we'll now need Casts and a lFoundry. \\n\\nTo start making the lFoundry, start with Fire Clay.]&f"]
	quest.6BBC440BD0AD0E93.title: "&9&l&d寂静装备&f&r与&c&l高效金属加工&7[lSilent Gear and lProductive Metalworks]&f"
	quest.6BFD7854F078BF16.quest_subtitle: "好好把握这个&7[Get a Grip on this]&f"
	quest.711826BBCA832EE2.quest_desc: ["所有&8铸模&r生而平等.换个说法,我的意思是它们的制作方法相同.\\n\\n通过在&8&a浇铸台&f&r上将&8钢水&r浇注到一个物品上!\\n\\n你问我们如何制作&8钢水&r？只需熔化任何&8钢&r物品或锭.或者你可以将9份&7铁&r与10份&0煤&r合金化.\\n\\n当&c&l铸造厂&r被&6加热&r且其中含有正确数量的不同&7液态金属&r时,合金化就会发生.这两种&7液态金属&r将结合成一种&7液态金属&r!\\n&7[All Casts are made equal. In another sense I mean they are made the same way. \\n\\nBy Pouring Steel onto an Item in a Casting Table! \\n\\nHow do we make Steel you ask? Simply Melt down any Steel Items or Ingots. Or you can Alloy 9 Iron to 10 Coal. \\n\\nAlloying will happen when the lFoundry is Heated and the right amounts of different Liquid Metals are in it. These two Liquid Metals will combine into one Liquid Metal!]&f"]
	quest.711826BBCA832EE2.title: "&8铸模&7[Casts]&f"
	quest.766C80E5D7B7A916.quest_subtitle: "选一个!&7[Pick one!]&f"
	quest.769D5DE66D13B256.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods 团队&r或&2社区贡献者&r创作,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均根据&e版权所有&r许可,未经&6AllTheMods 团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods 团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被有意隐藏,如果你看到此信息,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.7C3D763CF22D167A.quest_desc: ["&a星祭&f充能器可以为材料”附魔\\n&7[The Starlight Charger can \"enchant\" materials with the \"Star Charged\" enchantment.\\n\\nA structure must be built with the Starlight Charger in the middle in view of the night sky. It only gains Starlight Power during the night.\\n\\nThe Charger must be placed in the middle of a 7x7 structure, with a Pillar in each corner. Each pillar must have a \"Starlight Charger Cap\".\\n\\nIt also requires a charger catalyst per material.]&f"]
	quest.7C3D763CF22D167A.quest_subtitle: "”附魔”材料&7[\"Enchanting\" Materials]&f"
	quest.7C3D763CF22D167A.title: "&d星辉充能器&7[Starlight Charger]&f"
	quest.7D690A7D0FF6E328.title: "三级分级催化剂&7[Tier 3 Grader Catalyst]&f"
	quest.7E13007340A818C5.quest_desc: ["这是星辉充能器的一级支柱顶盖.\\n&7[This is a Tier 1 Pillar Cap for the Starlight Charger.]&f"]
	quest.7E13007340A818C5.title: "一级星辉充能器支柱顶盖&7[Tier 1 Starlight Charger Pillar Cap]&f"
	task.0EF203AF0BA514F7.title: "&a修理工具包&f&7[Repair Kits]&f"
	task.155D4ED18738E127.title: "熔炉储罐&7[Foundry Tanks]&f"
	task.2AE89914A34BF3AD.title: "&a火焰砖&f或熔炉玻璃&7[Fire Bricks or Foundry Windows]&f"
	task.3B23E744D3B72AE8.title: "&a火焰砖&f或熔炉玻璃&7[Fire Bricks or Foundry Windows]&f"
	task.511ECEA2E9BD1F71.title: "任意 #productivemetalworks:foundry_drains&7[Any #productivemetalworks:foundry_drains]&f"
	task.51297F6E0D9BB58C.title: "任意 #productivemetalworks:foundry_tanks&7[Any #productivemetalworks:foundry_tanks]&f"
	task.54EF988F476C9208.title: "熔炉排水口&7[Foundry Drains]&f"
	task.55E0635973A828B0.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6D9DBD885FE4C94C.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.76E296A2AD3EFE92.title: "任意 #productivemetalworks:foundry_controllers&7[Any #productivemetalworks:foundry_controllers]&f"
	task.7D9F2C8E7C65B654.title: "&a熔铸炉控制器&f&7[Foundry Controllers]&f"
	quest.00DB5495C3A44999.quest_desc: ["按住Shift并&a右击&f一个容器以清空.\\n&7[Shift-Right Click an inventory to empty.]&f"]
	quest.0108F3EFDFD6DFD0.quest_desc: ["&a存储&f连接器允许你连接多个未连接到存储&a控制器&f的存储单元,或连接到该控制器的任何方块.\\n\\n这是一种无线连接存储”多方块结构”的方式,无需右击每一个存储单元.\\n\\n14格的范围限制仍然适用.\\n&7[The Storage Link allows you to connect multiple storages that are not attached to a Storage Controller or any blocks that are connected to it.\\n\\nSo its a way to wirelessly connect a \"multiblock\" of storages without needing to right-click each one of them.\\n\\n14 blocks of range still applies.]&f"]
	quest.019CA0E35F888222.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.019CA0E35F888222.title: "&e高级补货升级&7[Advanced Restock Upgrade]&f"
	quest.0298A17C2AAC5765.quest_desc: ["使背包的堆叠上限增加8.\\n&7[Increases stack size in the Backpack by 8.]&f"]
	quest.0298A17C2AAC5765.title: "&b堆叠升级 三级&7[Stack Upgrade Tier 3]&f"
	quest.037415D5B965E214.quest_desc: ["此升级使背包不会损坏.\\n&7[This upgrade makes it so the Backpack can't die.]&f"]
	quest.0682DC1F2417DAEB.quest_desc: ["实用存储是一个存储模组,添加了各种有用的物品来帮助存储,以及存储大量相同物品的方法.\\n\\n这对于像圆石、泥土等物品非常有用.\\n&7[Functional Storage is a storage mod that adds varuious useful items to help with storage and ways of storing stacks of the same items.\\n\\nThis can be useful for items like Cobblestone, Dirt and more.]&f"]
	quest.0682DC1F2417DAEB.quest_subtitle: "&d储物抽屉&f的远亲&7[Storage Drawers Distant Relative]&f"
	quest.0682DC1F2417DAEB.title: "实用存储&7[Functional Storage]&f"
	quest.072FBEB0F6F1BC48.quest_desc: ["用于将抽屉连接到&a控制器&f,并连接&a末影抽屉&f.\\n\\n要将抽屉连接到控制器,请&a右击&f&a控制器&f方块开始配置.&a右击&f抽屉会将它们添加到网络中.\\n\\n手持此工具会显示哪些抽屉已连接到控制器.\\n&7[Used to link Drawers to a Controller and to link up Ender Drawers.\\n\\nTo link Drawers to the Controller, right click the Controller block to start configuration. Right clicking Drawers will add them to the network.\\n\\nHolding the tool will show you what Drawers are connected to the Controller.]&f"]
	quest.0CD04A00529FE1C9.quest_desc: ["可以制作&a铜箱子&f,但制作&a铁箱子&f并不需要它,不过如果你想节省一些铁,可以使用它.\\n&7[The Copper Chest can be made but is not needed to make an Iron Chest, it can be used if you want to save some Iron though.]&f"]
	quest.0CD04A00529FE1C9.title: "&6&a铜箱子&f&7[Copper Chest]&f"
	quest.0D4C64DD58567758.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个储罐.\\n&7[Adds a tank to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.0E057B7F76401421.quest_subtitle: "第一个升级&7[The First Upgrade]&f"
	quest.0E057B7F76401421.title: "&6&a铜背包&f&7[Copper Backpack]&f"
	quest.0E0CAA31480EC0A1.quest_desc: ["允许背包拾取物品.\\n&7[Allows the Backpack to pick up items.]&f"]
	quest.0E0CAA31480EC0A1.quest_subtitle: "允许背包拾取物品.&7[Allows the backpack to pick up items.]&f"
	quest.0E5AE195158CF344.quest_subtitle: "x32 存储升级&7[x32 Storage Upgrade]&f"
	quest.0E5AE195158CF344.title: "&d下界合金升级&7[Netherite Upgrade]&f"
	quest.110D27EA86CDA62B.quest_desc: ["将物品磁吸到背包中.\\n&7[Magnets items into the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.11A351E2CDE2A31E.quest_desc: [
		"集成终端还允许你无线访问你的存储!只需在任何连接你存储的逻辑缆线上安装一个来自&d动态联合/集成动力&f的全向分离器,\\n&7[Integrated Terminals also lets you access your storage wirelessly! Just attach an Omni-Directional Splitter from Integrated Dynamics on any Logic Cables connecting your storage, ]&f"
		"使用便携式&a存储终端&f&a右击&f,你现在就可以不受限制地访问你的系统.\\n&7[right click with the Portable Storage Terminal, and you now have unfettered access to your system.]&f"
	]
	quest.11A351E2CDE2A31E.title: "&a便携存储&f访问&7[Portable Storage Access]&f"
	quest.11D4EEAC61C7E530.quest_desc: ["&a收集&f升级将使抽屉从某一侧吸入物品.\\n&7[The Collector Upgrade will make the Drawer vacuum items in from one of the sides.]&f"]
	quest.11D57C768032E3F7.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.11D57C768032E3F7.title: "&e高级磁吸升级&7[Advanced Magnet Upgrade]&f"
	quest.122FBF5110E4CFF2.quest_desc: ["铁质降级会将抽屉的最大空间降为一组.这对于保持物品库存,但又不至于太多很有用.\\n&7[The Iron Downgrade will downgrade the Drawer's max space to a stack. This can be useful for keeping items on stock, but not too many.]&f"]
	quest.1310C1E14C259807.quest_desc: ["想要自定义抽屉外观？看这里,这些可以模仿一个方块的纹理作为外部,正面则使用不同的纹理.\\n\\n按照工具提示进行操作.\\n&7[Want to have custom Drawers? Look no further, these can mimic a block's texture on the outside, and a different one in the front.\\n\\nFollow the tooltip on how to do it.]&f"]
	quest.134608BB2B04D96E.quest_desc: ["箱子有27个槽位,可以制作成双箱以存储两倍的物品.\\n&7[Chests have 27 slots and can be made into a double chest to store twice that amount.]&f"]
	quest.134608BB2B04D96E.quest_subtitle: "箱子&7[The Chest]&f"
	quest.134608BB2B04D96E.title: "原版存储&7[Vanilla Storage]&f"
	quest.156FF8B7B724DC38.quest_desc: ["为进出背包的物品添加过滤器.\\n&7[Adds a filter for items being pumped in or out of the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.15CD4BFDC56E9510.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.15CD4BFDC56E9510.title: "&e高级&a工具交换器&f升级&7[Advanced Tool Swapper Upgrade]&f"
	quest.1659A59303C15CC9.quest_desc: ["木桶的工作原理与箱子相同,只是它们不能合并成一个.不过它们看起来更酷.\\n&7[Barrels work the same as Chests only they can't be combined together into 1. They look cool though.]&f"]
	quest.17DC77F7F8C68AE6.quest_desc: ["&a垃圾桶&f是一种销毁不需要的物品、流体和能量的方式.\\n&7[Trash Cans act as a way to destroy unwanted items, liquid, and power.]&f"]
	quest.17DC77F7F8C68AE6.quest_subtitle: "处理&a多余物品&f&7[Getting Rid of The Excess]&f"
	quest.17DC77F7F8C68AE6.title: "&a垃圾桶&f&7[Trash Cans]&f"
	quest.1985CFD1F0425E88.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.1985CFD1F0425E88.title: "&e高级拾取升级&7[Advanced Pickup Upgrade]&f"
	quest.19DFAEB6D88F3580.quest_desc: ["&a推动器&f升级允许抽屉向任意一侧推出物品.\\n&7[The Pusher Upgrade allows Drawers to push out items into any side.]&f"]
	quest.1A4B1CA7EC15348E.quest_desc: ["使用&a&a连接工具&f&r,你可以连接两个&a末影抽屉&f以同步它们的内容.\\n\\n这就像&a末影箱&f一样,但作为抽屉使用.\\n\\n要连接,先用&a&a连接工具&f&r右击第一个&a末影抽屉&f,然后左击第二个&a末影抽屉&f.\\n&7[Using a Linking Tool, you can link 2 Ender Drawers to sync up their contents.\\n\\nThis works just like an Ender Chest, but as a Drawer.\\n\\nTo link, right-click the first Ender Drawer with the Linking Tool, then left-click the second Ender Drawer.]&f"]
	quest.1A4B1CA7EC15348E.quest_subtitle: "维度抽屉...&7[Dimensional Drawer...]&f"
	quest.1A739D36D5E3B1AD.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.1A739D36D5E3B1AD.title: "&e高级喂养升级&7[Advanced Feeding Upgrade]&f"
	quest.1B72E95569B07E18.quest_subtitle: "x24 存储升级&7[x24 Storage Upgrade]&f"
	quest.1B72E95569B07E18.title: "&b钻石升级&7[Diamond Upgrade]&f"
	quest.1CACE201C6AA0913.quest_desc: ["此升级将在抽屉满时销毁多余的物品.\\n\\n这对于防止溢出或防止因存储已满而导致设置堵塞很有用.\\n&7[This upgrade will void extra items that come when Drawers are full.\\n\\nThis can be useful to prevent overflow or to prevent a setup from backing up due to the storage being full.]&f"]
	quest.1CD2C6AFD788C35E.quest_desc: ["将背包中的物品压缩为它们的2x2合成配方形式.\\n&7[Compacts items in the Backpack to their 2x2 recipe.]&f"]
	quest.1E499F94A2A193E1.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个&a爆裂熔炉&f界面.\\n&7[Adds a Blast Furnace GUI to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.1FE052F643401232.quest_desc: ["你需要这些来制作背包升级.\\n&7[You will need these to make Backpack Upgrades.]&f"]
	quest.1FE052F643401232.quest_subtitle: "升级的基础&7[The Base for Upgrades]&f"
	quest.1FE17B1C7C639F88.quest_desc: ["&a存储&f&a控制器&f允许你将多个存储单元当作一个大的存储多方块结构来操作.\\n\\n这允许建立一个非常大的存储网络,可以与诸如应用能源或&d动态联合/集成动力&f等模组结合,因为存储&a控制器&f充当了所有连接到它的存储单元的输入/输出点.\\n\\n连接可以通过简单地将存储单元放在存储&a控制器&f旁边,或放在已经连接到存储&a控制器&f的其他存储单元旁边来实现(这在所有方向上距离控制器最多14格内有效).\\n&7[The Storage Controller allows you to work with multiple storages as if they were one big storage multiblock.\\n\\nThis allows for a very large storage network, which can be combined with mods like Applied Energistics or Integrated Dynamics, as the Storage Controller acts as an in/out point for all storages attached to it.\\n\\nConnecting either can be done by simply putting storages next to Storage Controller or next to others that are already connected to Storage Controller (this works up to 14 blocks away from controller in all directions).]&f"]
	quest.209DC1E9AD4C5A84.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r为AllTheMods整合包创作.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e版权所有&r许可下,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.25AFD10D008DF30B.quest_desc: ["所有&a末影箱&f共享同一个库存,且该库存对每个玩家都不同.它们不能合并成一个.\\n&7[Ender Chests all share the same inventory and that inventory is different for every player. They can't be combined together into 1.]&f"]
	quest.26988E22BD019628.quest_desc: ["自动熔炼背包中的物品.\\n&7[Auto-smelt items in the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.26988E22BD019628.quest_subtitle: "自动化&7[Automatic]&f"
	quest.26988E22BD019628.title: "&e自动爆裂升级&7[Auto-Blasting Upgrade]&f"
	quest.26A9F402DAE15EA2.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个烟熏炉界面.\\n&7[Adds a Smoker GUI to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.2746575C929B6C50.quest_desc: ["抽屉可以是1x1、2x1或2x2.根据抽屉类型,可以容纳大量1/2/4种物品的堆叠.\\n&7[Drawers can be 1x1, 2x1 or 2x2. Drawers can hold a ton of stacks of 1/2/4 items depending on the type of Drawer.]&f"]
	quest.2746575C929B6C50.quest_subtitle: "堆叠再堆叠&7[Stacks on Stacks]&f"
	quest.289ED1DFD83B9838.quest_desc: [
		"你不仅可以连接物品,还可以连接流体!只需在任何存储流体的存储方案上放置一个流体接口,并用逻辑缆线连接,它就会出现在你的系统中!\\n&7[Not only are you able to connect items, you can also connect fluids! Just put a fluid interface on any storage solution that holds fluid and connect it with Logic Cables and it will appear in your system!]&f"
		""
		"与你的流体交互的一个便捷方法是:在物品栏中放好桶,点击流体,然后再点击桶来填充它们!\\n&7[A convenient way to interact with your fluid is by having buckets in your inventory and clicking in the fluid and then clicking again on the buckets to fill them!]&f"
	]
	quest.2B422B7E0CE3590D.quest_desc: ["&a压缩抽屉&f可以将放入其中的物品转换为其粒或块形态.\\n\\n例如:放入一个&a铁锭&f将允许你取出9个铁粒,或者如果放入更多铁,会将其转换为铁块.\\n&7[The Compacting Drawer can convert items placed inside to their nugget or block forms.\\n\\nFor example: An Iron Ingot placed in this will allow you to pull out 9 nuggets, or if more Iron is placed in, will covert it to Iron Blocks.]&f"]
	quest.2B422B7E0CE3590D.quest_subtitle: "自动压缩/解压&7[Auto Compacts/Decompacts]&f"
	quest.2F9B0C642A6BE30C.title: "&f&a铁质背包&f&7[Iron Backpack]&f"
	quest.2FC15D3916DBF4E4.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.2FC15D3916DBF4E4.title: "&e高级虚空升级&7[Advanced Void Upgrade]&f"
	quest.3043C83CCFC9706D.quest_desc: [
		"毫无疑问,在建立AE2之前最好的存储解决方案是&9集成终端&r.\\n&7[Undoubtedly the best storage solution before setting up AE2 is Integrated Terminals.]&f"
		""
		"&9集成终端&r为你提供了一个前期存储解决方案,\\n&7[Integrated Terminals provides you an early-game storage solution ]&f"
		"它允许你访问周围所有的箱子,以及一些自动合成选项!\\n&7[that allows you to access all surrounding chests, as well as some autocrafting options!]&f"
		""
		"首先,通过将玻璃放入装有门瑞尔树脂的&a烘干池&f中来制作一些门瑞尔玻璃.\\n&7[First, make some Menril Glass by putting Glass in a Drying Basin filled with Menril Resin.]&f"
	]
	quest.3043C83CCFC9706D.title: "集成终端&7[Integrated Terminals]&f"
	quest.33882172DA8021F6.quest_desc: ["用背包内的物品保持玩家物品栏堆叠满.\\n&7[Keeps the player's inventory stacked up from items inside the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.33AADC1B97E9F7A9.quest_desc: ["运输矿车是装有箱子的矿车.你不能乘坐它们,但它们对于通过铁路系统运输物品很有用.\\n&7[Minecarts with Chests are Minecarts with Chests in them. You can't ride in these but they can be useful for transporting items across Rail systems.]&f"]
	quest.36BCE35215B2B6E9.quest_desc: ["自动熔炼背包中的物品.\\n&7[Auto-smelt items in the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.36BCE35215B2B6E9.quest_subtitle: "自动化&7[Automatic]&f"
	quest.36BCE35215B2B6E9.title: "&e自动烟熏升级&7[Auto-Smoking Upgrade]&f"
	quest.38F9E9A830D3EA0C.quest_desc: ["如果你认为这个模组只用于存储物品,那你就错了,还有&a流体抽屉&f!\\n\\n它们的工作方式与普通抽屉相同,但存储的是流体.\\n&7[If you thought this mod was only for storing items, you would be wrong, there are also Fluid Drawers!\\n\\nThey work the same way as regular Drawers, but store fluids instead.]&f"]
	quest.3A1D07AED2A841E4.quest_desc: ["自动熔炼背包中的物品.\\n&7[Auto-smelt items in the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.3A1D07AED2A841E4.quest_subtitle: "自动化&7[Automatic]&f"
	quest.3A1D07AED2A841E4.title: "&e自动熔炼升级&7[Auto-Smelting Upgrade]&f"
	quest.3B570B3DB5F6D2CB.quest_subtitle: "x16 存储升级&7[x16 Storage Upgrade]&f"
	quest.3B570B3DB5F6D2CB.title: "&e金质升级&r&7[Gold Upgrade]&f"
	quest.3CE3CDB9C93CBDAD.quest_desc: ["[ \"Want to do some autocrafting? Check out the full \", { \"text\": \"IntegratedDynamics\", \"underlined\": true, \"clickEvent\": { \"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"499CF9F39CED8899\" } }, \" guide!\" ]"]
	quest.3CE3CDB9C93CBDAD.title: "自动合成&7[Autocrafting]&f"
	quest.3E33730DC2115D26.title: "&e&a金箱子&f&7[Gold Chest]&f"
	quest.4007DFA7CC3A5FF2.quest_desc: ["为了避免这个&o整个任务章节&r被升级项覆盖,请查看精妙背包的升级项.\\n\\n你需要制作&d精妙存储&f的对应物,但它们的功能大致相同.\\n&7[To save you from having this entire quest section covered with upgrades, take a look at the Sophisticated Backpack upgrades\\n\\nYou'll need to make the Sophisticated Storage equivalent, but they function about the same.]&f"]
	quest.4007DFA7CC3A5FF2.quest_subtitle: "升级的基础&7[The Base for Upgrades]&f"
	quest.45268A619787288F.title: "&e&a金质背包&f&7[Gold Backpack]&f"
	quest.46D756F4DC6CC894.title: "&d&a下界合金背包&f&7[Netherite Backpack]&f"
	quest.485D5664A17E16DF.quest_subtitle: "x8 存储升级&7[x8 Storage Upgrade]&f"
	quest.485D5664A17E16DF.title: "&6铜质升级&7[Copper Upgrade]&f"
	quest.4A854CD5EC70733E.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个工作台界面.\\n&7[Adds a Crafting Table GUI to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.4B62AF0405F68041.quest_desc: ["添加一个过滤器,允许你告诉背包应该保持哪些物品的库存.按住Shift右击一个容器会补充它.\\n&7[Adds a filter that allows you to tell the Backpack which items it should keep stocked. Shift right-clicking an inventory will refill it.]&f"]
	quest.4B62AF0405F68041.quest_subtitle: "全部备齐&7[All Stocked up]&f"
	quest.4C0BDD483CCB40C4.title: "&b&a钻石箱子&f&7[Diamond Chest]&f"
	quest.4C0EAB9F795686D0.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.4C0EAB9F795686D0.title: "&e高级存入升级&7[Advanced Deposit Upgrade]&f"
	quest.4C2A60FC1F1E0328.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个电池.\\n&7[Adds a battery to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.4E4C8BCD45766F03.quest_desc: ["此抽屉会自动将放入其中的物品转换为其压缩形态.\\n&7[This Drawer will auto convert the item placed inside it into it's compacted form.]&f"]
	quest.4E4C8BCD45766F03.quest_subtitle: "自动压缩/解压&7[Auto Compacts/Decompacts]&f"
	quest.508A8366219175FE.quest_desc: ["&a配置&f工具用于锁定抽屉,使其记住内部存放的物品.\\n\\n这在设置从抽屉推入和拉出物品的系统时非常有用.&a锁定&f的抽屉不会替换被锁定的物品!\\n&7[The Configuration Tool is used to lock Drawers for them to remember the item it has inside.\\n\\nThis can be useful whenever you set up a system to push and pull from Drawers. The locked Drawer will not replace the item that was locked on it!]&f"]
	quest.52672B7FFFD51D16.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个切石机界面.\\n&7[Adds a Stonecutter GUI to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.53F861876B991C36.quest_desc: ["为背包添加一个唱片机界面.\\n&7[Adds a Jukebox GUI to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.53F861876B991C36.quest_subtitle: "现在我们来点音乐&7[Now we're jammin]&f"
	quest.544791880F315D5A.quest_desc: ["运输船是装有箱子的船.你可以在船上时打开箱子,也可以右击它.一次只能有一个人乘坐这艘船.\\n&7[Boats with Chests are Boats with Chests on them. You can open the chest while you're in the Boat or you can right-click on it. Only one person can ride in the Boat at a time.]&f"]
	quest.56B80A7EBFE21428.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.56B80A7EBFE21428.title: "&e高级泵升级&7[Advanced Pump Upgrade]&f"
	quest.57CF8C6C867B9BDA.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.57CF8C6C867B9BDA.title: "&e高级过滤升级&7[Advanced Filter Upgrade]&f"
	quest.58514FDE153FD971.quest_subtitle: "&a铁箱子&f?&7[Iron Chests?]&f"
	quest.58514FDE153FD971.title: "&f&a铁箱子&f&7[Iron Chest]&f"
	quest.5A94A2664BFDD7B9.quest_desc: ["欢迎来到基础存储章节!\\n\\n你将找到所有无需能源即可存储物品的基础方法,以及满足你存储需求的有用物品!\\n&7[Welcome to the Basic Storage Chapter!\\n\\nYou'll find all of the basic ways to store items without needing power, as well as useful items for your storage needs!]&f"]
	quest.5A94A2664BFDD7B9.title: "基础存储&7[Basic Storage]&f"
	quest.5E4BC0F59C90433A.quest_desc: ["&d精妙存储&f允许你用金属升级你的箱子和木桶,以增加它们的存储容量!你还可以添加升级来增强它们的功能.\\n\\n这些箱子就像原版的箱子或木桶,但它们有一个用于放置存储升级的槽位!\\n&7[Sophisticated Storage allows you to upgrade your Chests and Barrels with metals to increase their storage! You can also add upgrades to increase their functionality.\\n\\nThese chests are just like a vanilla Chest or Barrel, but they have a slot for a Storage Upgrade!]&f"]
	quest.5E4BC0F59C90433A.quest_subtitle: "”原版箱子”&7[\"Vanilla Chest\"]&f"
	quest.5E4BC0F59C90433A.title: "&d精妙存储&f&7[Sophisticated Storage]&f"
	quest.5E4FE420B6D2C97F.quest_desc: ["将背包中的物品压缩为它们的3x3合成配方形式.\\n&7[Compacts items in the backpack to their 3x3 recipe.]&f"]
	quest.5E4FE420B6D2C97F.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.5E4FE420B6D2C97F.title: "&e高级压缩升级&7[Advanced Compacting Upgrade]&f"
	quest.5FA9BC0D8476D322.quest_desc: ["自动用背包中的食物喂食你.\\n&7[Auto-feeds you with food in the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.615B9062FE8CCD36.quest_desc: ["自动切换为对你正在观察的方块最有效的工具.\\n&7[Auto-swaps to the tool that is most effective for the block you are looking at.]&f"]
	quest.61A22707DBC83818.quest_desc: ["&a存储&f访问点连接到&a控制器&f时,充当存储&a控制器&f,能够被输入或输出物品.本质上是抽屉网络的入口点.\\n&7[The Storage Access Point acts as a Storage Controller when linked to it, being able to be pushed into or pulled from. Basically a entry point for the Drawers.]&f"]
	quest.668C313FF46B6005.quest_desc: ["为背包添加熔炉GUI.\\n&7[Adds a Furnace GUI to the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.67704F7341EDCC49.title: "&b&a钻石背包&f&7[Diamond Backpack]&f"
	quest.696E063016CAD1B9.quest_desc: ["为你的背包添加Chipped工作台的合成GUI.\\n&7[Adds crafting GUIs for Chipped Workbenches to your Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.6A2B2C5E2ADCE366.quest_desc: ["&a精妙背包&f提供可升级的背包,可以使用过滤器来添加精巧的功能!\\n\\n背包可以放在你的Curios背部槽位中,并且可以被染色.\\n&7[Sophisticated Backpacks offers upgradable Backpacks that can use filters to add nifty features!\\n\\nBackpacks can be put in your Curios Back slot and they can be dyed.]&f"]
	quest.6A2B2C5E2ADCE366.quest_subtitle: "物品栏太小了&7[Inventories are too Small]&f"
	quest.6A2B2C5E2ADCE366.title: "&a精妙背包&f&7[Sophisticated Backpacks]&f"
	quest.6E3D53D1C4569A89.quest_desc: ["允许在你和背包之间泵送经验.\\n&7[Alloes you to pump experience between you and the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.6E3D53D1C4569A89.quest_subtitle: "存储经验&7[Storing XP]&f"
	quest.6E3D53D1C4569A89.title: "&a&a经验泵&f升级&7[Experience Pump Upgrade]&f"
	quest.6E9041744C592573.quest_desc: ["增加从储罐升级中泵送液体的能力.\\n&7[Adds the ability to pump liquids from the Tank Upgrade.]&f"]
	quest.6F6A23579CAE8013.quest_desc: [
		"接下来,继续制作一些物品接口和逻辑线缆.\\n&7[Next, go ahead and make some Item Interfaces and Logic Cables.]&f"
		""
		"将接口放置在你想要连接的箱子上,并使用逻辑线缆将它们全部连接起来.\\n&7[Place the Interfaces on chests you want to connect, and use Logic Cables to connect them all.]&f"
		""
		"然后你只需要在上面放一个&a存储终端&f,瞧!你就可以访问你的整个存储系统了.\\n&7[Then all you have to do is slap a Storage Terminal on there and voilà! You have access to your entire storage system.]&f"
	]
	quest.6F6A23579CAE8013.title: "连接你的存储&7[Connecting Your Storage]&f"
	quest.6FBAE89EE782DABA.quest_desc: ["当放置并用&a&a连接工具&f&r与其他抽屉连接时,&a控制器&f充当”枢纽”.\\n\\n如果你双击右键它,你物品栏中所有在抽屉网络中有对应槽位的物品都会被吸入.\\n\\n通过潜行右键单击控制器(空手),你可以打开升级标签页,向那些槽位添加普通的存储升级以增加控制器的范围.最大范围是所有方向40格,或一个80x80x80的立方体.\\n&7[When placed and connected with the Linking Tool to other Drawers, the Controller acts as a \"Hub\".\\n\\nIf you double right-click this, all the items in your inventory that have a slot in the Drawer network will be pulled.\\n\\nBy sneak right-Clicking the controller with an empty hand, you can open the upgrades tab, add normal storage upgrades to those slots to increase the Controller's range. Max range is 40 blocks for all sides, or a cube of 80x80x80.]&f"]
	quest.6FBAE89EE782DABA.quest_subtitle: "抽屉的大脑&7[The Brain of the Drawers]&f"
	quest.70902EF96F060672.quest_desc: ["此升级将使抽屉在所有面输出红石信号,信号强度表示其满/空程度.\\n\\n对于多槽位抽屉,可以配置升级以监控哪个槽位.\\n\\n0 - 表示空.\\n15 - 表示满.\\n&7[This upgrade will make Drawers output a Redstone signal on all sides, signal strength saying how full/empty it is.\\n\\nFor multi-slot Drawers, the upgrade can be configured to which slot to monitor.\\n\\n0 - means empty.\\n15 - means full.]&f"]
	quest.7649D648A3688D4A.quest_desc: ["抽取升级允许抽屉从任何面吸入物品.\\n&7[The Puller Upgrade allows Drawers to pull in items from any side.]&f"]
	quest.77F241BEE9902751.quest_desc: ["&d精妙存储&f中最大的箱子\\n&7[The biggest of the chests from Sophisticated Storage]&f"]
	quest.77F241BEE9902751.quest_subtitle: "活动空间真大!&7[So much room for activities!]&f"
	quest.77F241BEE9902751.title: "&d&a下界合金箱子&f&7[Netherite Chest]&f"
	quest.785951190FFDAA21.quest_desc: ["将背包中的堆叠大小增加4.\\n&7[Increases stack size in the Backpack by 4.]&f"]
	quest.785951190FFDAA21.title: "&e堆叠升级 等级 2&7[Stack Upgrade Tier 2]&f"
	quest.78E51D22C16C4686.quest_desc: ["&a存储&f &a控制器&f也能够无线连接到其他存储设备,这可以通过使用存储工具实现,只需&a右击&f存储&a控制器&f来绑定它,然后&a右击&f存储设备来链接它们.\\n\\n无线链接的范围与常规相同,为14格空间.\\n&7[The Storage Controller is also able to connect to other storages wirelessly, this is possible using the Storage Tool, just right click the Storage Controller to bind it and right click the storages to link them.\\n\\nThe range for wireless linking is the same as regular, 14 blocks of space.]&f"]
	quest.7AE3C8134F5ED726.quest_desc: ["将背包中的堆叠大小增加16.\\n&7[Increases stack size in the Backpack by 16.]&f"]
	quest.7AE3C8134F5ED726.title: "&d堆叠升级 等级 4&7[Stack Upgrade Tier 4]&f"
	quest.7C07D6A33F7ADB02.quest_desc: [
		"这是一个背包升级,让你可以把背包放进你的背包里.\\n&7[This is a Backpack upgrade so you can put your Backpack in your Backpack.]&f"
		""
		"这样你就可以在需要把背包放进背包里的时候,把你的背包放进背包里.\\n&7[So you can have your Backpack in your Backpack for when you need your Backpack in your Backpack.]&f"
	]
	quest.7C07D6A33F7ADB02.quest_subtitle: "背包里的背包？&7[Backpacks in your Backpacks?]&f"
	quest.7C0F7A1B3AB9A1A1.quest_subtitle: "更多过滤选项&7[More Filtering Options]&f"
	quest.7C0F7A1B3AB9A1A1.title: "&e高级补充升级&7[Advanced Refill Upgrade]&f"
	quest.7E9E03274A88347D.quest_desc: ["将背包中的堆叠大小增加2.\\n&7[Increases stack size in the Backpack by 2.]&f"]
	quest.7E9E03274A88347D.title: "&f堆叠升级 等级 1&7[Stack Upgrade Tier 1]&f"
	quest.7EF57BBEAA4B6B08.quest_desc: ["想使用像&9&d应用能源2&f&r这样的模组创建虚拟存储吗？\\n\\n这些是升级存储的好方法,但重要的是要谈谈&eNBT物品&r以及存储它们的最佳方式.\\n\\nNBT物品是附有额外标签的物品.附魔物品、有耐久度的物品等等.这些都是附有NBT标签的物品.因此,它们通常无法堆叠.\\n\\n当你将大量此类物品存储到像AE2这样的存储系统中时,你可能会给你的存档或服务器带来问题.\\n\\n因此,最好将它们存储在箱子或袋子里!\\n&7[Looking to create virtual storage using a mod like Applied Energistics 2?\\n\\nThese are great ways to upgrade your storage, but it is important to talk about NBT Items and the best way to store them.\\n\\nNBT items are items with extra tags attached to them. Enchanted items, items with durability and more. These are items with NBT tags attached to them. Because of this, they don't usually stack.\\n\\nWhen you store a lot of these into a storage system like AE2, you run the chance of creating issues for your save or server.\\n\\nBecause of this, it is best to store them in Chests or Bags!]&f"]
	quest.7EFBFF5D0DA018E7.quest_desc: ["为背包中添加一个用于自动删除物品的过滤器.\\n&7[Adds a filter for items you want to auto-delete in the Backpack.]&f"]
	quest.7EFBFF5D0DA018E7.quest_subtitle: "为背包中添加一个用于自动删除物品的过滤器.&7[Adds a filter for items you want to auto-delete in the backpack.]&f"
	quest.7F990FBC1A691020.quest_desc: ["陷阱箱与普通箱子相同,只是在打开时会发出红石信号,并且它们不能组合在一起成为一个.\\n&7[Trapped Chests are the same as regular Chests only the emit a Redstone signal when opened and they can't be combined together into 1.]&f"]
	quest.7F990FBC1A691020.quest_subtitle: "”我想知道这里面有什么？”&7[\"I wonder what's in here?\"]&f"
	task.00ED02255105A973.title: "&a钻石箱子&f&7[Diamond Chests]&f"
	task.0427B441A750316F.title: "&a金箱子&f&7[Gold Chests]&f"
	task.073D1C45B3018BBA.title: "箱子&7[Chests]&f"
	task.14FA4A933C39A406.title: "运输船&7[Boats with Chests]&f"
	task.1809DDEA104A9CE8.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.200CE35BF3C04F6F.title: "&a铜箱子&f&7[Copper Chests]&f"
	task.21FBC4E0F668347C.title: "NBT与你!&7[NBT and YOU!]&f"
	task.26A85DCA60F71DFF.title: "&a流体抽屉&f&7[Fluid Drawers]&f"
	task.2E04D0F6EEABE677.title: "抽屉&7[Drawers]&f"
	task.301665A6315B569C.title: "存储控制器&7[Storage Controllers]&f"
	task.349B2DA0A38AE9B5.title: "&a镶框抽屉&f&7[Framed Drawers]&f"
	task.34B6EB0B801E4743.title: "&a下界合金箱子&f&7[Netherite Chests]&f"
	task.49F46466DB8EDD61.title: "&a铁箱子&f&7[Iron Chests]&f"
	task.51CC9A8E36385400.title: "箱子&7[Chests]&f"
	task.593CD1E685B4DDAA.title: "Chipped升级&7[Chipped Upgrades]&f"
	task.5DEBE38C614EFBB4.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6205B6B93B306A12.title: "箱子&7[Chests]&f"
	quest.0152938EE5651409.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e版权所有&r许可下,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.0790D3BB481162A6.quest_desc: [
		"需要一个便携工作台？那便携&a锻造台&f怎么样？\\n&7[Need a portable Crafting Table? How about a portable Smithing Table? ]&f"
		""
		"&l&8合成&a便携工具&f&r添加了一些你最喜欢的合成站的便携版本!这是游戏早期必备品.\\n&7[lCrafting On A Stick adds portable versions of some of your favorite crafting stations! This is a must have in the early game.]&f"
	]
	quest.0790D3BB481162A6.quest_subtitle: "少放置,多合成&7[Less Placing, more Crafting]&f"
	quest.0790D3BB481162A6.title: "合成……在棍子上!&7[Crafting... on a Stick!]&f"
	quest.0C856BBB1679A7DD.quest_desc: ["在本页,你将找到一些有用的物品和信息来帮助你的旅程!\\n&7[On this page, you'll find some useful items and info to help you on your journey!]&f"]
	quest.0C856BBB1679A7DD.quest_subtitle: "以及其他有用物品!&7[And Other Useful Items!]&f"
	quest.0F8F37D7E12078F5.quest_subtitle: "完成所有提示!&7[Complete all the tips!]&f"
	quest.219AA017149C36E2.quest_desc: ["陷阱商人地毯会立即杀死任何在它附近生成的流浪商人!\\n\\n这些可能是整个整合包中最好的物品.\\n&7[Trapped Trader Carpets will kill any Wandering Traders that spawn near it instantly!\\n\\nThese might be the best items in the entire pack.]&f"]
	quest.219AA017149C36E2.quest_subtitle: "不再有烦人的商人!&7[No more Annoying Traders!]&f"
	quest.32ECD93A8F2FAB8F.quest_desc: ["&6喷气背包&r是一种备受喜爱的移动方式.\\n\\n要开始制作它们,你需要从&6木制喷气背包&r开始!这可以一直升级到&5&a创造喷气背包&f&r.\\n\\n虽然它有许多版本,但工作原理都相同.它们都可以放在你的&a胸甲栏&f、背部饰品槽或饰品槽中.\\n\\n它们也都需要FE才能工作,你可以使用任何物品充电器为它们充电!它们会消耗FE来飞行,是的,如果能量耗尽你会掉下来.\\n要飞行,你需要打开引擎(V),然后当你按住空格键时你会向上飞,松开时会下降.\\n\\n对于那些不喜欢下降的人,你可以打开悬停(默认未绑定),开启后你将在同一高度飞行；能够用(空格键)升高,用(Shift键)降低.\\n\\n要调整飞行速度,请更改你的油门.默认减少油门是(,),增加油门是(.)!\\n&7[Jetpacks are a beloved way of getting around. \\n\\nTo start making them you'll need to start with a Wood Jetpack! This can be upgraded all the way to a Creative Jetpack. \\n\\nWhile it does have many versions each work all the same. They all can be placed in your Chestplate Slot, or Back Curio, or Curio Curio. \\n\\nAll of them also need FE to work, you can use any Item Charger to charge them! They will use FE to fly and yes you will drop if you run out of Energy. \\nTo fly you'll need to turn on your Engine (V), then when you hold Space you'll fly up and drop when you let go. \\n\\nFor those who don't enjoy dropping, then you can turn on Hover (Unbinded), when set on you will Fly at the same altitude; being able to go higher with (Space) and lower with (Shift). \\n\\nTo adjust how fast you fly, change your Throttle. Decreasing it is (,) by default and increasing it is (.) by default!]&f"]
	quest.32ECD93A8F2FAB8F.title: "&l&6&d&a铁质飞行背包&f&f&7[lIron Jetpacks]&f"
	quest.3B4BF42C55C8BBBF.quest_desc: ["你是不是很讨厌在破坏东西时,方块掉落在你刚好够不到的地方!\\n\\n那么不用担心,因为我们有&4磁铁&r!只需在手持&4磁铁&r时&a右击&f即可打开它.然后,5格半径内所有掉落的物品和方块都会飞向你.\\n\\n你也可以将&4磁铁&r装备在你的Curios槽位中以持续使用它!\\n\\n如果你不希望继续使用&4磁铁&r(我发现这在&a刷怪塔&f附近会发生),只需再次&a右击&f它即可禁用.\\n\\n它也可以升级以增加范围!\\n&7[Don't you hate when your breaking something and the Blocks fall just out of your reach! \\n\\nWell worry no more for we have Magnets! Simply Right Click while holding the Magnet to turn it on. Then, all dropped Items and Blocks in a 5 Block Radius will come to you. \\n\\nYou can also equip the Magnet in your Curios to keep using it! \\n\\nIf you don't wish to continue using the Magnet (I find this happens near Mob Farms) then just Right Click with it again to disable it. \\n\\nIt can also be upgraded to increase the range!]&f"]
	quest.3B4BF42C55C8BBBF.title: "&l&9简易&4磁铁&7[lSimple Magnets]&f"
	quest.5EE945A1185E8336.quest_desc: ["&l&7实用存储&r添加了&7抽屉&r,可以容纳数堆物品.这些可以升级以容纳更多堆!\\n\\n这对于你大量获得的物品非常有用,比如圆石或种子!\\n&7[lFunctional Storage adds Drawers that can hold several stacks of an item. These can be upgraded to hold even more stacks!\\n\\nThis is great for items you get a lot of, like Cobblestone or Seeds!]&f"]
	quest.5EE945A1185E8336.quest_subtitle: "&d储物抽屉&f?&7[Storage Drawers?]&f"
	quest.5EE945A1185E8336.title: "&l&7实用存储&r&7[lFunctional Storage]&f"
	quest.637981B64BBE0D92.quest_desc: ["&a充电站&r是一个非常实用的&a游戏早期&f方块.\\n\\n它显然用于&a充电&f物品.既可以输入能量,也可以使用熔炉燃料以FE的形式产生能量.\\n\\n然后,你可以将任何需要&a充电&f的物品放入最右侧的槽位.\\n&7[The Charging Station is a very helpful Early Game Block. \\n\\nIt is clearly used for charging Items. Either Pipe in Energy or use Furnace Fuel to make Energy in the form of FE. \\n\\nThen, you can put any Item that needs charging into the Right most Slot.]&f"]
	quest.637981B64BBE0D92.title: "&l&a&a充电小帮手&f&7[lCharging Gadgets]&f"
	quest.722978AC0C1B2649.quest_desc: ["轻松实现无限&9水&r自动化的物品.\\n\\n需要更多&9水&r？再做一个!\\n&7[Easy item to automate infinite water. \\n\\nNeed more water? Make another!]&f"]
	quest.722978AC0C1B2649.quest_subtitle: "&a适用于&f反应堆冷却剂&7[Can be used as Reactor Coolant]&f"
	quest.722978AC0C1B2649.title: "无限&9水&r&7[Infinite Water]&f"
	quest.7A514E27E1A7FE32.quest_desc: ["钻石也允许我们使用&l&c&d建筑小帮手&f&r模组创建一些很酷的小工具来帮助我们建造.\\n\\n这些是帮助你建造更大基地,或使用&c&a破坏小帮手&f&r清理空间的好工具.\\n\\n此外,你可以用与链接无线终端相同的方式将它们链接到AE2网络,使用无线访问点.这允许它使用存储在ME网络中的方块.\\n&7[Diamonds also allow us to create some cool gadgets to help us build using the mod lBuilding Gadgets.\\n\\nThese are great tools to help you build bigger bases, or for clearing out space using the Destruction Gadget.\\n\\nAdditionally, you can link them to an AE2 Network with the same way you link Wireless Terminals, with the Wireless Access Point. This allows it to use blocks stored in the ME Network.]&f"]
	quest.7A514E27E1A7FE32.title: "&l&c&d建筑小帮手&f&r&7[lBuilding Gadgets]&f"
	quest.7EC8814940C4C3D7.quest_desc: ["使用此物品来缩小.有助于自动化工作,也很有趣.\\n&7[Use this item to shrink. Helpful for working on automation and also just overall fun.]&f"]
	quest.7EC8814940C4C3D7.quest_subtitle: "亲爱的,我把自己缩小了&7[Honey I Shrunk Myself]&f"
	quest.7EC8814940C4C3D7.title: "&a个人缩放设备&f&7[Personal Shrinking Device]&f"
	task.172162127C8F6E4E.title: "任意商人地毯&7[Any Trader carpet]&f"
	task.3B1F1A7CAC8B7BC7.title: "抽屉&7[Drawers]&f"
	task.3DC008A578A93CCF.title: "提示与技巧!&7[Tips and Tricks!]&f"
	task.42DA8E971B27ACED.title: "倾囊相授&7[Tipped Out]&f"
	task.47A1F59A538E3C4B.title: "&d建筑小帮手&f&7[Building Gadgets]&f"
	task.4AEB792F6A939B3A.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.6038387EA35404CD.title: "棍子上的合成&7[Crafting on a Stick]&f"
	task.6A965CD027BF762F.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	quest.3708A4780ACEB34E.quest_desc: ["在此整合包中,任务是可选的.模组不会因为完成任何任务而被锁定!\\n\\n主线任务线之外的许多独立任务线旨在作为模组指南.如果你想遵循进度,请务必查看主线任务线!\\n&7[In this modpack, quests are optional. Mods are not gated behind completing any quests!\\n\\nA lot of the individual questlines outside of the Main questline are meant to serve as mod guides. If you want to follow the progression, make sure to check out the Main Questline!]&f"]
	quest.3BC0A50886A3222B.quest_desc: ["ATM10 &a向天空进发&f是一个大杂烩整合包,允许你以自己的方式探索各种不同的模组!\\n\\n如果你有任何问题或疑问,请随时加入ATM的Discord!\\n&7[ATM10 To the Sky is a kitchensink pack that allows you to explore a variety of different mods in your own way!\\n\\nIf you have any questions or issues, feel free to join the ATM discord!]&f"]
	quest.3BC0A50886A3222B.title: "&d欢迎来到All The Mods 10,现在在天空(再次)&7[Welcome to All The Mods 10, Now in the Sky (again)]&f"
	quest.49EDAA2F57D3BF1D.quest_desc: ["此任务由&6AllTheMods Staff&r或&2社区贡献者&r编写,用于AllTheMods整合包.\\n\\n由于所有&6AllTheMods&r整合包均在&e版权所有&r许可下,未经&6AllTheMods团队&r明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非&6AllTheMods团队&r发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被故意隐藏,如果你看到这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.5AC1BE754210429E.quest_desc: ["如果你想为你和你的朋友创建一个团队,使用命令&a/ftbteams party create (团队名称)&r来创建团队!\\n&7[If you want to create a team for you and your friends, use the command /ftbteams party create (name of team) to create the team!]&f"]
	task.201F519941A2C7F4.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.2C816285392535F0.title: "版权所有&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
	task.4F13A02FB0055A62.title: "创建团队&7[Creating a Team]&f"
	task.52BB142F044075B4.title: "任务&7[Quests]&f"
	quest.030AC1AF8F735550.quest_desc: ["要将液体输入储罐,你需要某种管道.\\n\\n水力泵可以以缓慢的速度自动将水输入其中,而且是免费的!\\n&7[To get liquids into the Tank you'll need some sort of Pipes.\\n\\nThe Hydro Pump can automatically put Water into them at a slow rate, but also for free!]&f"]
	quest.030AC1AF8F735550.title: "管道&7[Pipes]&f"
	quest.06B85804163DD18B.quest_desc: ["索林箱(Soaryn是&dXY工艺&f的作者)是&dXY工艺&f的箱子.\\n\\n破坏方块时它不会掉落其中的物品!我想知道它上面的那些方块是做什么用的？\\n&7[The Soaryn Box (Soaryn being the author of XyCraft) is the chest of XyCraft.\\n\\nIt will not hold items off breaking the block! I wonder what those squares on it do?]&f"]
	quest.08E484DD3E751697.quest_subtitle: "Roy G. Biv 中的 B&7[The B in Roy G. Biv]&f"
	quest.08E484DD3E751697.title: "&b蓝色 XY 宝石&7[Blue Xychorium Gems]&f"
	quest.0D01524F249E25D7.quest_subtitle: "谁把灯关了？&7[Who turned off the lights?]&f"
	quest.0D01524F249E25D7.title: "&8暗色 XY 宝石&7[Dark Xychorium Gems]&f"
	quest.15540271BF17C2E4.quest_desc: ["&l欢迎来到 &dXY工艺&f!&r\\n\\n这个系列模组主要致力于 &dXY工艺&f:世界与机器!\\n”世界”部分为我们提供了可以通过筛矿获得的宝石.\\n&7[lWelcome to XyCraft!\\n\\nThis series of mods is mostly dedicated to XyCraft: World and Machines!\\nWorld gives us the Gems which can be obtained by sieving.]&f"]
	quest.15540271BF17C2E4.title: "&l&dXY工艺&f&7[lXyCraft]&f"
	quest.16B4A00948D1F60D.quest_desc: ["此任务由 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 或 &2社区贡献者&r 创作,用于 AllTheMods 整合包.\\n\\n由于所有 &6AllTheMods&r 整合包均采用 &e保留所有权利&r 许可,未经 &6AllTheMods 团队&r 明确许可,此任务不得用于任何非 AllTheMods 团队发布的公开整合包.\\n\\n此任务被有意隐藏,如果你看到了这个,说明你正处于编辑模式.\\n&7[This Quest has been authored by AllTheMods Staff, or a Community contributor for use in AllTheMods Modpacks.\\n\\nAs all AllTheMods packs are licensed under All Rights Reserved, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by AllTheMods Team without explicit permission.\\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode.]&f"]
	quest.1E00DBAACDF4404F.quest_desc: ["&a收集器&f 可以作为一个非常廉价的 &a漏斗&f.\\n\\n它会拾取 3 格半径内的所有物品,并将其放入下方或自身的物品栏中.它可以用红石信号关闭!\\n&7[The Collector works as a very cheap Absorption Hopper.\\n\\nIt will pick up all items within a 3 block radius and put it in the inventory below or it's own. It can be turned off with Redstone!]&f"]
	quest.2278A98DCDF713D7.quest_desc: ["现在是制作储罐的时候了!首先你需要建筑方块和至少 1 个阀门.玻璃和物品输入输出口是可选的.\\n\\n储罐必须由建筑方块构成框架.建筑方块是指任何不透明、不受重力影响、且非自然生成的泥土或草方块.\\n\\n石头、木头或金属等方块必须构成框架和边缘.玻璃、阀门和物品输入输出口必须放置在墙壁上,内部必须是空心的.\\n\\n它最大只能为 13x13x13 大小.完成所有步骤后,&a右击&f 阀门,它会显示”已形成”或告诉你问题所在.\\n&7[Now it's time to make the Tank! First off you need Building Blocks and at least 1 Valve. Glass and Item IOs are optional.\\n\\nThe Tank must be made of a frame of building blocks. Building blocks are anything that isn't transparent, gravity influenced, or natural Dirt or Grass.\\n\\nItems like stone, wood, or metal must make the frame and the edges. Glass, Valves, and Item IOs must be placed in the walls and the inside must be hollow.\\n\\nIt can only be 13x13x13 big. Once you done all that, right click the Valve and it will either say 'Formed' or will tell you the problem.]&f"]
	quest.2278A98DCDF713D7.title: "&l储罐&7[lThe Tank]&f"
	quest.2AC7BC448C007BDB.quest_desc: ["用铝加固基维石,你将得到制作机器所需的 &a机器框架&f.\\n&7[Reinforce the Kivi with Aluminum and you'll get Machine Frames which are needed to craft machines.]&f"]
	quest.2B5E14A47062F83C.quest_subtitle: "Roy G. Biv 中的 R&7[The R in Roy G. Biv]&f"
	quest.2B5E14A47062F83C.title: "&c红色 XY 宝石&7[Red Xychorium Gems]&f"
	quest.2C4ECA4F5B1639F4.quest_desc: ["光照场不会发出太多光,但它确实像一个 &a巨型火把&f 一样工作.\\n\\n怪物不会在它周围设定的区域内生成.该区域半径约为 32 格.\\n&7[The Light Field doesn't show much light, but it does work like a Mega Torch.\\n\\nMobs won't spawn in a set area around it. That area is about a 32 block radius.]&f"]
	quest.2C4ECA4F5B1639F4.title: "&f光照场&7[Light Field]&f"
	quest.2C7D62231AD6406A.quest_desc: ["&dXY工艺&f 有一个很棒的 &a流体储罐&f 多方块结构!\\n&7[XyCraft has a great Fluid Tank mulitblock!]&f"]
	quest.2C7D62231AD6406A.title: "&b流体存储与操控&7[Fluid Storage and Manipulation]&f"
	quest.355244420EA47546.quest_desc: ["装配机是自动合成器.它会从下方的物品栏中取出物品,并按照设定的配方进行合成.\\n\\n你可以通过按住 CTRL 点击来锁定配方.不过,它需要将合成出的物品用管道输出.\\n&7[Fabricator is the Auto-Crafter. It will take items from the inventory below and make a set recipe.\\n\\nYou can lock recipes with CTRL Click. It will need to pipe out the created items though.]&f"]
	quest.355244420EA47546.quest_subtitle: "自动合成器&7[Auto-Crafter]&f"
	quest.39E4FC9BA89E44BC.quest_desc: ["&a气球&f 拴绳是一种早期且有限制的创造模式飞行来源.\\n\\n放下拴绳,你就会被拴在一个气球上!双击空格键开始飞行,只是不能飞太远.飞得太远,你就会脱离并坠落.\\n&7[The Balloon on a Stick is an early and restrictive source of Creative Flight.\\n\\nPlace down the stick and you'll be attached to a balloon! Double touch space to start Flying just not too far. Go too far and you'll get detached and fall.]&f"]
	quest.39E4FC9BA89E44BC.quest_subtitle: "飞起来!&7[Up!]&f"
	quest.3E970E76372AB094.quest_desc: ["&2加速种植器&r 的工作原理与普通耕地类似,但有一些变化.\\n\\n它会自动浇水,并且比普通耕地更快.\\n&7[The Accelerated Planter works similar to normal Farmland but with some changes.\\n\\nIt's automatIically watered and it's faster than normal Farmland.]&f"]
	quest.3E970E76372AB094.title: "&2加速种植器&7[Accelerated Planter]&f"
	quest.3F68BA498E877C8C.quest_subtitle: "Roy Biv 的中间名&7[Roy Biv's middle name]&f"
	quest.3F68BA498E877C8C.title: "&a绿色 XY 宝石&7[Green Xychorium Gems]&f"
	quest.43F08B510FC1C06F.quest_desc: ["物品输入输出口使我们能够将物品运输进出储罐.它们可以切换为输出或输入模式.\\n&7[Item IOs give us the ability to transport items in and out of the Tank. They can be toggled for Output and Input.]&f"]
	quest.43F08B510FC1C06F.quest_subtitle: "物品的进出口&7[Where Items come and go]&f"
	quest.43F08B510FC1C06F.title: "物品输入输出口&7[Item IOs]&f"
	quest.4A92237E17ED5F1C.quest_desc: ["虚空容器可以将任何物品栏变成 &a垃圾桶&f.把它放在物品栏上方,物品就再也不会堆积了!\\n&7[The Void Container makes any inventory a Trash Can. Put it on top of the inventory and no more items!]&f"]
	quest.5E1D4169C083ACEF.quest_desc: ["&c点火板&r 在接收到 &a红石信号&f 时,会在其前方生成火焰.\\n\\n当信号停止时,它会熄灭火焰.\\n&7[The Ignition Plate spawns fire infront of it when given a Redstone Signal.\\n\\nIt will put out the fire when the Signal is stopped.]&f"]
	quest.5E1D4169C083ACEF.title: "&c点火板&7[Ignition Plate]&f"
	quest.623E6A855B363C8D.quest_desc: ["&9水方块&r 具有水的特性,但没有流动的部分.\\n\\n可以用它们制作 &a造石机&f,可以用它浇灌耕地,只是你不能用它来落地水.(鱼也会试图进入其中,但仍然会死亡).\\n&7[The Water Block acts as Water without the whole moving part.\\n\\nCobble Gens can be made with them, Farmland can be watered with it, you just can't MLG clutch with it. (Fish will also try to get into it but will still die).]&f"]
	quest.623E6A855B363C8D.quest_subtitle: "固态的水？冰？&7[Water but Solid, Ice?]&f"
	quest.623E6A855B363C8D.title: "&9水方块&7[Water Block]&f"
	quest.643FB1A3ED0EA9EC.quest_desc: ["阀门是你储罐的核心.你将在这里泵入或通过管道输入流体.\\n&7[The Valve is the Heart of your Tank. This is where you'll pump, or pipe fluids into it.]&f"]
	quest.643FB1A3ED0EA9EC.quest_subtitle: "流体的进出口&7[Where Fluid comes and goes]&f"
	quest.643FB1A3ED0EA9EC.title: "阀门&7[Valves]&f"
	quest.64D0D69ADB8820DA.quest_desc: ["&8&a流体虚空&f&r 是一个会消除所有与其相连的水的方块.\\n\\n水源方块或流动的水,任何在 1 格半径范围内的水都会消失.\\n&7[The Fluid Void is a block that stops all water connected to it.\\n\\nSource blocks or flowing water, anything within a 1 block radius is gone.]&f"]
	quest.64D0D69ADB8820DA.title: "&8&a流体虚空&f&7[Fluid Void]&f"
	quest.69F11A94D44AB5CF.quest_subtitle: "&a非常多&f 的光!&7[Too much light!]&f"
	quest.69F11A94D44AB5CF.title: "&f亮色 XY 宝石&7[Light Xychorium Gems]&f"
	quest.6D0876A402C22067.quest_desc: ["&dXY工艺&f 有一些物品存储和操控功能.不过,没有流体存储和操控那么多!\\n&7[XyCraft has some item storage and manipulation. Not as much as fluid storage and manipulation though!]&f"]
	quest.6D0876A402C22067.title: "&6物品存储与操控&7[Item Storage and Manipulation]&f"
	quest.71D133BA3EC6F4FD.quest_desc: ["&a提取器&f 会”生长”其下方的方块或物品,并将其移动到上方的物品栏中.\\n\\n这可以用于制作适用于多种石头的圆石生成器、紫水晶生成器,甚至是 &a龙蛋&f 生成器,以及其他用途!\\n&7[The Extractor will \"grow\" the block or item beneath it and move it to an inventory above it.\\n\\nThis can be used for a Cobblestone generator that works with many types of stone, an Amethyst generator, or even a Dragon Egg generator, along with others!]&f"]
	quest.71D133BA3EC6F4FD.quest_subtitle: "开采岩石!(以及更多)&7[Farming for Rocks! (and More)]&f"
	quest.7574A782DCFB87CE.quest_desc: ["基维石可以用于几件事,主要是装饰和机器.\\n\\n你将需要基维石来制作 &dXY工艺&f 中的 &a机器框架&f 和其他机器.它可以与 XY 宝石一起在切石机中制作装饰性方块.\\n&7[Kivi can be used for a couple of things, mainly for decorations and machines.\\n\\nYou'll need Kivi for Machine Frames and other machines in XyCraft. It can be used with Xychorium Gems in a Stonecutter for decorative blocks.]&f"]
	quest.7574A782DCFB87CE.title: "&l&7基维石&7[lKivi]&f"
	task.4EEF358CAC170CC4.title: "XY 宝石&7[Xychorium Gems]&f"
	task.55DD09212E3DB168.title: "&a流体传输管道&f&7[Fluid Pipes]&f"
	task.706FA543A6C675D3.title: "保留所有权利&7[AllRightsReserved]&f"
}
